var descriptions = new Array();
descriptions["2828"]={cn:"如果你热衷于将万物焚烧成焦土，并且喜欢聆听煤炭燃烧的嘶嘶声胜过陪女友逛街，那么蚍斯博将是你的最佳伴侣。身为火焰独角仙族的一员，蚍斯博最爱玩火。他生性冲动易怒，随时都有可能暴起伤人。尽管如此，蚍斯博却更喜欢从远程出其不意地攻击敌人。蚍斯博肯定会让你的敌人浑身冒烟！",en:"If you\'re a supporter of scorched earth tactics and prefer to hear coal sizzling than grasshoppers chirping, then you\'ll have a friend in Beelzebug. Just as fiery (though not quite as evil) as his name suggests, this sidekick lives to play with fire. Despite being aggressive, impulsive and liable to blow his top at any moment, he still keeps his distance so he can strike enemies like a bolt from the blue. Beelzebug will make your enemies break into a sweat, and with good reason... He\'s on fire!"};
descriptions["2829"]={cn:"鲨卡尔最显著的特征是他细长的牙齿。他就像军校里讨人厌的教官一样，粗鲁，但公正不阿。有鲨卡尔做队友，即便身处险境也完全不用担心。他会始终激励你，踢你的屁股，逼你前行。必要的时候，他甚至会以身犯险，保你周全。此外，鲨卡尔还特别喜欢引敌人上钩...！",en:"The first thing people notice about Skale is that he\'s a little long in the tooth. He\'s like the drill sergeant you love to hate: harsh, but fair! With Skale at your side, you don\'t need to worry about being thrown in the deep end: he\'s right there to motivate you and improve your performance, and, if necessary, dive in to drag you to safety. Besides all that, he\'s quite partial to netting a few enemies himself...!"};
descriptions["2830"]={cn:"梦想有个职业沙包代你承受无脑骑士之怒？你需要的是浩兰克。他外表温顺平和，内心却渴望着原始狂野的混战！千万别以为他只会双脚插地，站着挨打，你一定没有见过他在战场里赤裸上身，只穿一条裤衩特技全开的样子。敌人完全不知道他从哪里发起了攻击！",en:"Are you looking for someone to get beaten to a pulp on your behalf? Then Trank\'s the sidekick you need: he may be calm by nature, but he\'ll never say no to a good old-fashioned scrap! If you think he\'ll just plant his roots in the soil and wait for the attacks to roll in, you\'ve obviously never seen him in acrobat mode on the battlefield. Your enemies won\'t know what hit \'em!"};
descriptions["2831"]={cn:"鹰克斯天性活泼好动，从来不会在一处停留太久。他脚步如飞，战斗起来无影无踪。鹰克斯从来不是有耐性的人...如果拿他的鸟头开太多玩笑的话，你很有可能会被发射到半空中...也有可能是墙上。只要发现鹰克斯，敌人多半只会撒腿逃跑...前提是他们逃得掉！",en:"Fast and fickle, Krobax never stays in one place for long. It can be difficult keeping up with him, but his flighty ways are part of his charm! He\'s not exactly patient with people... If you take the \'birdbrain\' jokes too far, you\'re likely to find yourself catapulted up into the air... or into a wall. If your enemies don\'t want to get caught up in the commotion, they\'ll keep well away... if they can, that is!"};
descriptions["2832"]={cn:"如果你视重铸秩序与和谐为己任，那么你需要真正的领袖气质！身为M战警的领袖，狸米诺始终关心盟友的安危。他是弱者、受压迫者以及一切急需帮助的人的守护神。他拥有睿智的大脑、活泼的心灵以及助人为乐的品格。然而，狸米诺有个唯一的污点，就是他的哥哥影武...",en:"If you take it upon yourself to restore lost harmony and re-establish order in the Krosmoz, you\'d better hope you\'ve got the charisma to pull it off! Leader of the Multimen, Lumino is always there to care for his brothers and allies whenever they get a booboo. Defender of all who are weak, oppressed and in need, he\'s as bright and lively as he is generous. In fact, the only thing wrong with Lumino, the only dark stain on his dazzling character sketch, is his brother Shadow..."};
descriptions["2833"]={cn:"有光就有影。你正面对着一只真正的阴影恶魔。\n历经绝望的折磨，影武彻底臣服于黑暗。他与世界格格不入，破坏是他生存的唯一理由。影武偶尔也会被你逗笑；然而，只要敌人一出现，影武就会立刻变得异常冷血。",en:"Now here\'s a sidekick who puts the emo back in demon! Tormented by the futility of existence, Shadow decided to turn to the dark side. Destruction is his only reason for staying in a world where he has never truly felt alive. A smile from you might be enough to make him feel a little more positive, but whenever your enemies appear, Shadow gets mean... really mean."};
descriptions["2867"]={cn:"无论你身陷何种险境，佣兵队长都会给你有力支援。佣兵队长隶属于阿斯图布某个威望极高的组织。他们是阿斯图布忠诚的守护者，深信攻击才是最好的防御，甚至因此饱受有勇无谋的责骂。这就是佣兵队长的信条：如果还可以进攻，就绝不停留防守。",en:"Whatever mess you manage to get yourself into, this sidekick has got your back. He\'s a valiant knight who belongs to an order respected all over Astrub. Often dubbed \'dauntless and irreproachable\', these fervent defenders of Astrub know that attack is the best defence. That\'s right: if he can help it, this sidekick will be dealing the blows, not taking them."};
descriptions["3065"]={cn:"在萨弗基亚周围广袤的海域里，你可以钓到很多稀奇古怪的东西，不过其中最怪的无疑是蒸汽原型机。更别提人们在大洋深处发现了为数众多的原型机，而且这些机器竟然还能使用！\n尤其是它的种种细节毫无争议地表明，大名鼎鼎的雾霾克斯伯爵与其有着千丝万缕的联系。这种机器显然（至少在考古学家眼里是这样）是蒸汽行者的原型。但是与我们现在所熟知和喜爱的蒸汽行者大不相同。\n是的。蒸汽原型机是“初代”蒸汽行者的一项创造。似乎这些机器出现于某段特殊时期，正是那时蒸汽行者开始分化为两大分支：\n - 一部分选择继续信仰欧塔波达，愿意一直保持凡人之躯过平静的生活，别无他求。\n - 而另一部分掌控了毁灭之力，并按照自己的意志创造出机械躯体，达到了延长生命的目的。他们就是我们现今见到的蒸汽行者。\n蒸汽原型机的发现给十二世界的科学魔法界带来了一系列疑问：\n这种机器的制造者是现在蒸汽行者的祖先，还是信仰欧塔波达的另一分支？这种复杂的装置内是否有“人”的存在？机器中的幽灵？为什么会有这么多蒸汽原型机？它们是战争机器吗？莫非它们是蒸汽行者用来安置灵魂的容器，从未被使用过？蒸汽原型机如何自我修复？它们的动力源是什么？\n没人敢把一个“启动”的蒸汽原型机拆开来一探究竟。虽然专家已经把仅有的“未启动”的残破样本拆得四分五裂，并从各个角度检查一番，但结果却一无所获。唯一可以确定的是，它们不像现代蒸汽行者一样使用毁灭之力作为动力。\n著名的原型机学家伊萨克·阿东莫夫提出了一个更加玄乎的疑问：基于什么缘由，一旦一台原型机被人类启动，他就会绝对效忠并誓死保护这名人类？其中似乎有着某种无形的原则...所谓的原型机三大定律？\n天知道...",en:"Of all the weird things you can fish out of the open seas around Sufokia, the Protoflex is definitely the weirdest. And even more troubling than the number of these machines that have been found in the area\'s ocean depths is the fact that most of these things are still entirely operational!\nEspecially considering how certain of its details call to mind the famed Sire Flexington, to whom it owes its name, this machine is clearly (at least to the Archaosologists) of Foggernaut origin. But not the Foggernauts we all know and love.\nNo. The Protoflex is a creation of the \"original\" Foggernauts. It seems the machine is from the exact period in time when the Foggernauts split into two factions:\n - One side who continued to believe in Oktapodas, and were OK with living their lives with mortal bodies and nothing more.\n - The other, the Foggernauts that we know today, who learned to master Stasis and created mechanical bodies to host their minds and prolong their lives.\nAll this has led to some questions for the World of Twelve\'s scientomagi:\nWas this mechanism built by the ancestors of our mechanical Foggernauts, or the other Foggernaut faction? Is there \"someone\" inside this complex device? A ghost in the machine? Why were there so many Protoflexes? Were they war machines? Were they some sort of receptacle for Foggernaut souls and simply never used? How do the Protoflexes repair themselves? What is their power source?\nNo one has dared to take apart an \"active\" Protoflex, and although the rare \"inactive\", damaged specimens have been taken apart by experts and examined from every angle, nothing has been learned. The only thing that is certain is that they aren\'t powered by Stasis, like modern Foggernauts.\nAnd Asiic Amivos, noted protologist, has proposed this last, unnerving question that scientists are a bit scared of answering: Why does an activated Protoflex attach itself to a person and protect them, even to the point of putting its own existence at risk, as if it was following some sort of rule, or law...? The laws of prototics?\n\nMaybe some day we\'ll find out..."};
descriptions["3071"]={cn:"酷洛晶体是异次元旅者理想的宠物。它们由旅者们亲手创造，自龙蛋时代开始经过了几个世纪的改良。酷洛晶体从曾经的通讯和防卫工具演变成现在每一位异次元旅者不可分割的左膀右臂。它是一种取之不尽的能量源，同时也兼具多种功能：防御力、攻击力、治疗能力、传送能力、通讯功能、可根据环境条件调整发光强度、身份识别系统、生物感应型保安系统...\n每个酷洛晶体都按其主人的喜好进行过不同性质的改良，赋予了独一无二的能力。你所获得的这种酷洛晶体虽为泛用型，但仍然与广受好评的基本型具有完全相同的特征。",en:"The Krosmoglob is the ideal pet for Dimensional Voyagers. Created by them, and lovingly improved over the course of several centuries since the Dofus Era, the Krosmoglob - previously nothing more than a means of communication and defense - has become an extension of any self-respecting Dimensional Voyager.\nIt\'s an almost limitless source of energy, as well as integrated armor, attack skills, heals, teleportation, communication, and variable ambient lighting from soft romantic to glaringly bright, an identification system, biometric security...\nEach Krosmoglob was improved by its owner, giving them each unique skills. The one you\'ve picked up is pretty generic, but still offers the same features as the basic model that was proven to be a great success."};
descriptions["3075"]={cn:"当萨迪达神创造半植物半娃娃的菲拉茜雅时，他并没意识到这个娃娃竟能如此迅速地自我繁殖。菲拉茜雅·毒叶能够独自创造新的生命体，她所到之处嫩芽丛生。\n后来，一群凡人闯入萨迪达神域，无意间将一些嫩芽带到了十二世界。\n如果你像萨迪达神对待菲拉茜雅那样无微不至地照料嫩芽，最后她将蜕变成一位忠实得力的助手。不过不要指望她会像仆人一样温顺谦卑，因为毒叶不论生死都是敌人的眼中钉肉中刺。",en:"When the god Sadida created Filacia, a half-doll, half-plant, he didn\'t realize how quickly she was going to be able to multiply and spread. The Treacherose can create new beings all by herself, and causes seedlings to sprout wherever she goes.\nThe story goes that a few of these shoots were brought back to the World of Twelve by some mortals visiting Sadida\'s divine dimension.\nIf a shoot is treated with as much care and attention as the original Filacia was by Sadida, a faithful, devoted sidekick will bloom. Just don\'t expect her to be a docile servant, because Treacheroses live (and die) to be thorns in their enemies\' sides."};
descriptions["3081"]={cn:"次元先知，天赋异禀的她想出了一个极为复杂的计划来抹除自己的记忆，借此隐藏神之力，保证它不会落入众神手中。她探索神域，寻找自己的本源，与斯拉姆神本人面对面地较量。险些救了你的性命之后，她决定让你参与她的任务。",en:"The Explorancient, gifted as she is, devised an elaborate plan to erase her own memory to hide the Divine Power out the Gods\' reach. She explored the Divine Dimensions to discover her origins and found herself confronted by Sram in person. Having saved you by a hair, she\'s decided you should join her on her quest."};
descriptions["3084"]={cn:"绝命小径黑帮的前任首领，他渗入潘朵拉的小队，替黑暗君上监视他们的一举一动。旅途过程中，他渐渐体会到同伴间的羁绊。当黑暗君上决定消灭他们时，他挺身而出。最后，他在与斯拉姆神的战斗中侥幸逃生，决定成为你的同伴，补偿以往的过错。",en:"Former leader of the Tethdrap gang, he infiltrated Pandora\'s group in order to monitor their movements on behalf of Dark Master Wilby. During their travels, he came to appreciate the company of the group, and when his master decided to eliminate them, he stepped in. Finally spared after the confrontation with Sram, he\'s decided to accompany you to make amends with honour."};
descriptions["3575"]={cn:"精通风元素的迷雾骑士是控场大师，能准确定位、移动他的敌人和同伴。他能以意想不到的方式跨越地形造成大量伤害，同时为他的团队做出重要的支援和辅助。\n\n几百年来，作为杀手、佣兵、强盗和保镖，黑暗骑士组织一直以可怕的声名为世人所知。他们是一脉相承的优秀战士，能通过他们最喜爱的武器——折磨者来增强自己对元素的掌控能力。这些不可思议的手枪可以将使用者的元素之力汇聚起来，然后以惊人的力量发射出去。最初的黑暗骑士是五个与众不同的兄弟：烈焰、浊流、迷雾、青叶和暗夜。步入青年时，他们发觉了自己的力量，之后养父为他们分别制造了折磨者。黑暗骑士们慢慢变得强大而叛逆，最后在暗影的带领下杀害他们养父，逃离了邦塔。\n没人知道黑暗骑士后来怎么样了。据说折磨者代代相传，新的黑暗骑士也随之诞生，不知道这算是一种祝福亦或是一种诅咒。可谁又敢揭开黑暗骑士的面具，看看六百年之后面具下的是否还是相同的面孔呢？",en:"Specialized in the Air element, the Cloud Knight is a master in the art of control, terrain, and positioning his enemies as well as his allies. He\'s capable of inflicting heavy damage across an area in unexpected ways, all while filling the crucial support frole for his team.\n\nWorking as assassins, mercenaries, brigands and bodyguards, the Dark Knights have had a fearsome reputation for hundreds of years. From a long line of exceptional fighters, they are able to enhance their mastery of the elements through their favorite weapon—the Tormentator. These magical pistols channel and focus the user\'s elemental power and shoots it out with devastating force. The original Dark Knights were peculiar children, five brothers: Flame, Drop, Cloud, Leaf and Shadow. They discovered their powers when they reached adolescence and each received a specially created Tormentator from their adoptive father. Lead by Shadow, the Dark Knights became consumed with their power and rebelled, killing their adoptive father before fleeing to Bonta.\nNo one knows what became of the five Dark Knights. It is said that new generations of Dark Knight are created as these Tormentators are passed down over the years, although whether this a blessing or curse is a matter of opinion. But who knows and who would dare find out if the people behind the Dark Knights\' faceless masks are any different from the original five from 600 years ago?"};
descriptions["3577"]={cn:"精于火元素的烈焰骑士是破坏大师，能令自己的同伴和敌人都陷入熊熊烈焰中。他可以灼烧目标，立即造成大量伤害，同时也能随着时间的推移造成额外伤害。\n\n几百年来，作为杀手、佣兵、强盗和保镖，黑暗骑士组织一直以可怕的声名为世人所知。他们是一脉相承的优秀战士，能通过他们最喜爱的武器——折磨者来增强自己对元素的掌控能力。这些不可思议的手枪可以将使用者的元素之力汇聚起来，然后以惊人的力量发射出去。最初的黑暗骑士是五个与众不同的兄弟：烈焰、浊流、迷雾、青叶和暗夜。步入青年时，他们发觉了自己的力量，之后养父为他们分别制造了折磨者。黑暗骑士们慢慢变得强大而叛逆，最后在暗影的带领下杀害他们养父，逃离了邦塔。\n没人知道黑暗骑士后来怎么样了。据说折磨者代代相传，新的黑暗骑士也随之诞生，不知道这算是一种祝福亦或是一种诅咒。可谁又敢揭开黑暗骑士的面具，看看六百年之后面具下的是否还是相同的面孔呢？",en:"Specialized in the Fire element, the Flame Knight is a master in the art of damage and can set both his allies and enemies on fire. He inflicts major damage instantly by burning his targets, which also causes extra damage over time.\n\nWorking as assassins, mercenaries, brigands and bodyguards, the Dark Knights have had a fearsome reputation for hundreds of years. From a long line of exceptional fighters, they are able to enhance their mastery of the elements through their favorite weapon—the Tormentator. These magical pistols channel and focus the user\'s elemental power and shoots it out with devastating force. The original Dark Knights were peculiar children, five brothers: Flame, Drop, Cloud, Leaf and Shadow. They discovered their powers when they reached adolescence and each received a specially created Tormentator from their adoptive father. Lead by Shadow, the Dark Knights became consumed with their power and rebelled, killing their adoptive father before fleeing to Bonta.\nNo one knows what became of the five Dark Knights. It is said that new generations of Dark Knight are created as these Tormentators are passed down over the years, although whether this a blessing or curse is a matter of opinion. But who knows and who would dare find out if the people behind the Dark Knights\' faceless masks are any different from the original five from 600 years ago?"};
descriptions["3578"]={cn:"精通水元素的浊流骑士是支援大师，善于治疗、强化自己的同伴。他的技能可以在造成伤害的同时支援自己的同伴。\n\n几百年来，作为杀手、佣兵、强盗和保镖，黑暗骑士组织一直以可怕的声名为世人所知。他们是一脉相承的优秀战士，能通过他们最喜爱的武器——折磨者来增强自己对元素的掌控能力。这些不可思议的手枪可以将使用者的元素之力汇聚起来，然后以惊人的力量发射出去。最初的黑暗骑士是五个与众不同的兄弟：烈焰、浊流、迷雾、青叶和暗夜。步入青年时，他们发觉了自己的力量，之后养父为他们分别制造了折磨者。黑暗骑士们慢慢变得强大而叛逆，最后在暗影的带领下杀害他们养父，逃离了邦塔。\n没人知道黑暗骑士后来怎么样了。据说折磨者代代相传，新的黑暗骑士也随之诞生，不知道这算是一种祝福亦或是一种诅咒。可谁又敢揭开黑暗骑士的面具，看看六百年之后面具下的是否还是相同的面孔呢？",en:"Specialized in the Water element, the Drop Knight is a master in the art of support, healing, and providing bonuses for his allies. He\'s equally capable of dealing damage while supporting his teammates in optimal ways.\n\nWorking as assassins, mercenaries, brigands and bodyguards, the Dark Knights have had a fearsome reputation for hundreds of years. From a long line of exceptional fighters, they are able to enhance their mastery of the elements through their favorite weapon—the Tormentator. These magical pistols channel and focus the user\'s elemental power and shoots it out with devastating force. The original Dark Knights were peculiar children, five brothers: Flame, Drop, Cloud, Leaf and Shadow. They discovered their powers when they reached adolescence and each received a specially created Tormentator from their adoptive father. Lead by Shadow, the Dark Knights became consumed with their power and rebelled, killing their adoptive father before fleeing to Bonta.\nNo one knows what became of the five Dark Knights. It is said that new generations of Dark Knight are created as these Tormentators are passed down over the years, although whether this a blessing or curse is a matter of opinion. But who knows and who would dare find out if the people behind the Dark Knights\' faceless masks are any different from the original five from 600 years ago?"};
descriptions["4453"]={cn:"希波拉瑞是位技巧熟练的土匪，他的笑容以及优美旋律的魅力虏获了许多人。\n\n现在这位潇洒的绅士打算加入你的团队，用他的音乐创作照亮你的日子。他的演奏对于所有人都适用，并可以适应任何状况：无论是欢乐或阴郁的时光，希波拉瑞知道该所演奏及该所说。他通常会边唱歌边跳舞，他熟练的舞步吸引着群众掏出他们的钱包– 而他们卡玛的叮当声，轻柔地与他后跟的踏地声回响着。\n\n他曾让许多人心碎，没错，但那其中一颗心曾牢牢地缠绕在他身上...\n\n在那眼镜及眼影之下，这位多彩多姿的角色看来埋藏着一段过往，比他那土匪头套下的面容更为深暗且神秘。",en:"Hippolyre is a very skilled Riktus. He\'s charmed many with his smile and his sweet melodies.\n\nNow this jaunty gent has decided to join your company to brighten your days with his music-making. His repertoire has something for everyone, and he can adapt to any situation: whether it\'s party time or the mood is more somber, Hippolyre knows just what to play and what to say. He often accompanies his songs with some dancing, his deft footwork enticing the crowd to lighten their purses and the clinking of their kamas gently echoes the tapping of his heels.\n\nHe was a heartbreaker, all right, but one of the hearts he won had stuck with him...\n\nBeneath the spectacle and the eye-shadow, this colorful character seems to be hiding a past that\'s even more dark and mysterious than what\'s under his Riktus hood."};
descriptions["12"]={cn:"传奇刺客卡尼·阿什所铸造的武器，来去无踪，见血封喉。也许这柄剑并不应该留在他手上...",en:"This sword was forged by the legendary Karne Aj, a Sram warrior known for being able slice quicker than his shadow. Letting him keep this weapon probably wasn\'t the wisest idea."};
descriptions["102"]={cn:"102",en:"102"};
descriptions["103"]={cn:"103",en:"103"};
descriptions["104"]={cn:"104",en:"104"};
descriptions["1718"]={cn:"虽然表面颗粒明显，苹朵木仍然深受雕刻家喜爱。他们能在一夜之间将这块无用的东西变成桌椅。太棒了！",en:"Though it\'s very grainy, Apiwood is quite popular with sculptors. They can turn a single branch of this useless stuff into table and chairs overnight. Fantastic!"};
descriptions["1719"]={cn:"能为苹朵派增添原汁原味的大自然芬芳，面点师都爱它。",en:"The bakers adore it: it gives that authentic natural flavor to their Api Pies."};
descriptions["1723"]={cn:"白蜡木有着久经考验的抗衰老的功能。同时也有利尿作用。",en:"Ash Wood has proven anti-aging properties. You just have to be able to put up with the diuretic effects."};
descriptions["1732"]={cn:"闻起来和榛子一样，很奇怪。榛木甚至和榛子有相同的纹理。唯一的不同是你咬榛子的时候不会掉牙齿。",en:"Hazel Wood smells just like Hazelnut, oddly enough. It also has the same texture. The only difference is that you won\'t lose any teeth biting into a Hazelnut."};
descriptions["1734"]={cn:"一天一个苹朵，医生...烦不烦啊老是这句话！",en:"\"Eat up your Apiz.\" Ah yes, everyone remembers that Bontarian chef\'s catchphrase. Some say he was the greatest troop motivator ever to scream a repetitive non-sequitur. Another favorite of his was \"An Api a day keeps the undertaker away.\""};
descriptions["1746"]={cn:"阿玛克纳国民十分喜欢榛子。他们甚至被称为果壳脑袋。然而他们不以为耻，反以为荣。",en:"Amaknians love these little hazelnuts so much that being known as the village nutcase has become a matter of intense pride."};
descriptions["1750"]={cn:"你永远数不清大麦粒到底能做成几样东西：面包、糖浆、面糊...实在太多了！",en:"It\'s amazing what you can make with a bit of barley grain: bread, syrup, a mess... The possibilities are almost endless!"};
descriptions["1752"]={cn:"小麦是随处可见的作物，同时也是各式食谱中的必备原料。正因为如此，反而搞不懂小麦的使用方法，最后只好往路过的无辜路人脸上扔。",en:"Wheat can be found pretty much everywhere and it\'s become a staple in cooking recipes. So much so, that you\'ll run out of things to do with it and might start throwing it out of the window at unsuspecting passers-by for fun."};
descriptions["1783"]={cn:"精致小巧的蘑菇，切成条状最好吃。",en:"This exquisite little mushroom tastes best when cut into fine strips."};
descriptions["1786"]={cn:"用淀粉勾芡过的玉米种子。",en:"Corn Seeds are packed with starch."};
descriptions["1832"]={cn:"不要被诱人的外表欺骗了...实际上难吃极了！",en:"Don\'t be fooled by the inviting, juicy, delicious, alluring color of these Gorsegoyle Berries... They\'re disgusting!"};
descriptions["1846"]={cn:"整天敲碎石是个不错的锻炼方法，还能帮助养成健壮的体魄。",en:"Smashing rocks all day is great exercise and it builds an iron constitution."};
descriptions["1848"]={cn:"石英广泛用于制作武器及机械时钟。",en:"Quartz is widely used for making weapons and mechanical clocks."};
descriptions["1851"]={cn:"铜矿导热性极佳。当你和漂亮姑娘在一起的时候，可以准确测量你的体温。",en:"Copper Ore gets its color from its excellent thermal conductivity. Perfect for taking your temperature when you\'re in the company of an attractive adventurer."};
descriptions["1853"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["1856"]={cn:"对于任何热衷于制造重型武器的武器大师来说，皇家铁矾土是一种高档原料。",en:"Royal Bauxite is a prized component for any weapons master interested in creating heavy weapons."};
descriptions["1863"]={cn:"红宝石是工匠的梦想。",en:"Rubies are a forger\'s dream: This is where the expression \"taking rubies for spinel\" comes from."};
descriptions["1886"]={cn:"埋下种子，收获属于你的艳丽卷心菜。",en:"Plant this seed for your very own voluptuous Babbage."};
descriptions["1889"]={cn:"菊芋能够发电是众所周知的特性。如果你刚从沉睡中醒来，你就恰好需要一根这个...和一名植物术士。",en:"The artichoke is known for its energizing properties. It\'s highly sought-after by Sadidas who\'ve just woken up from a deep sleep... and those in need of one."};
descriptions["1902"]={cn:"卷心菜：蜗牛们和变异虫的真爱所在。",en:"Babbage: the one true love of Snailmets and Larvae."};
descriptions["2021"]={cn:"小心了，女士们！它会撕咬一切东西！花边围巾、羊毛衫甚至披肩都难逃其口。说不定也只是个传说？",en:"Watch out ladies, it seems this thing chews everything it comes across! Lacy shawls, woolly sweaters, and even leather clavicle-warmers have all been known to get a nibbling. Or is it all just tall talk?"};
descriptions["2022"]={cn:"这个戒指曾属于古老世界的救世主包子·光年。他总是提起一家叫做“超越极限”的小酒馆。",en:"This ring once belonged to the renowned Bouze Lite Yeah, the savior of the ancient World. His favorite sentence was about some Inn or another called the \"Finity and Beyond.\""};
descriptions["2023"]={cn:"穿上它们，再也不用担心会踩到绵球便便。因为两者闻起来都一样。",en:"With these boots, you no longer have to worry about stepping in Gobball dung. The smell will be exactly the same, either way."};
descriptions["2024"]={cn:"由绵球的残羹剩饭制成。是的，你没看错。绵球又不会刷盘子。",en:"This cloak was made from the remains of a Gobball\'s dinner. Yes, you read right. Sometimes even Gobballs don\'t clear their plates."};
descriptions["2025"]={cn:"又松又软的腰带...厚实的内衬，让冒险者相信自己已经装备精良。",en:"This puffy and soft belt is a real temptation... Less secure adventurers benefit from the extra padding to make others believe they\'re better equipped than they are."};
descriptions["2026"]={cn:"有人说这顶头盔能预知恋爱运势。",en:"Some say that the two horns on this hat can predict how your love life will turn out. That\'s one good reason to watch where you\'re sitting!"};
descriptions["2027"]={cn:"不仅仅会砸东西，还会到处乱咬。如果你相信上述描述的话，你得一直盯着...",en:"This hammer doesn\'t just like to smash things, it likes to bite them, too. And, if you believe that, you must need your head looking at..."};
descriptions["2035"]={cn:"挂在腰间才能显示出它的真正用处。",en:"If you manage to get this amulet around your waist you will unleash its true powers."};
descriptions["2036"]={cn:"豆芙妮用的高档货。你是豆芙妮吗？",en:"The height of class for the Tofoones. But are you a Tofoone though?"};
descriptions["2037"]={cn:"传说这柄剑是由一只豆芙打造的！它一定像你一样好骗...",en:"It is rumored that this sword was forged by a Tofu! He must have been very talented, indeed! Almost as talented as you are gullible, in fact..."};
descriptions["2038"]={cn:"轻量、实用，淡淡的黄色...由豆芙羽毛制成，大师级手笔！",en:"Light, useful, and a soft yellow... Tofu feathers exist for the sole purpose of making this cloak!"};
descriptions["2039"]={cn:"轻若无物。好像你自己也变轻了...",en:"This belt is scarily light. It seems anything hidden behind it becomes weightless..."};
descriptions["2040"]={cn:"现在它属于你了。你居然没有挖掉豆芙的眼睛，真糟糕，你也太无耻了...",en:"This Tofu skull becomes you perfectly. Too bad you didn\'t remove the eyes, it looks a little too cheeky..."};
descriptions["2041"]={cn:"在春天的田原里发足狂奔，像个发情的豆芙一样横冲直撞！没什么好害羞的。",en:"Mad races across spring fields, stampeding like a thousand rutting Tofus! It\'s good not to be afraid of looking silly."};
descriptions["2044"]={cn:"由100%可回收原料制成。护肩不能保护你，但是至少你问心无愧。",en:"Made from 100% recyclable materials, these epaulettes will not protect you, but at least you\'ll have a clear conscience."};
descriptions["2048"]={cn:"哇呀呀...",en:"Eeenie, meenie, minie, mo, Catch a... Galgarion by the toe?"};
descriptions["2057"]={cn:"轻若无物，经常让人忘了它是块盾牌。当然，这也有可能是因为它并不提供多少防护...",en:"This shield is so light you sometimes forget it\'s there to protect you! Though maybe that\'s because it\'s not doing such a great job of it..."};
descriptions["2058"]={cn:"牧羊杖的升级版。这把魔杖提供了更多驱使绵球群攻击敌人的方法。",en:"This is an improved version of the Shepherd\'s Staff. This wand now has even more ways of driving your flock to chop up your enemies."};
descriptions["2089"]={cn:"如果你发现有豆芙在你的背后跑来跑去，不要害怕！他们只是觉得你是他们的同类！",en:"If you see Tofus running after you when you\'re wearing these epaulettes, fear not! They just think you\'re one of them!"};
descriptions["2090"]={cn:"啊，这块盾牌明显已经干掉一个可怜虫了...",en:"Ah, this shield has clearly already taken one victim..."};
descriptions["2145"]={cn:"用拳头可抓不住苍蝇，但是可以打扁它。",en:"You couldn\'t hurt a fly with that fist of yours, but you might as well lash out anyway."};
descriptions["2175"]={cn:"别再傻傻地双手插口袋了，它们还可以用来放别的东西。",en:"Don\'t just stick your hands in there, use them for something useful."};
descriptions["2198"]={cn:"这根小巧的时钟指针被铭刻在了豆芙的骨头里。千万不要把它和真正的豆芙脆骨搞混了。",en:"This small, pointy clock hand was carved in Tofu bone. Please don\'t confuse it with actual Tofu on the Bone, which is a culinary specialty."};
descriptions["2214"]={cn:"轻便的帽子，可是不适合你的大头。",en:"Despite its lightness, this hat won\'t be able to do anything for you if you have a big head. Quite the opposite, in fact."};
descriptions["2243"]={cn:"木板是物品制作中的理想原料。通过10级伐木制作，可用于21-35级装备等用品制作。",en:"This plank is just fantastic, a pure wooden specimen. And very flat too."};
descriptions["2246"]={cn:"看见这堆羊毛，人们第一反应居然不是洁白、纯洁这样的形容词，对此精神脆弱的绵球们有点小伤心。",en:"White isn\'t the first word that springs to mind when you see this wool, but don\'t forget that Gobballs are very sensitive creatures..."};
descriptions["2248"]={cn:"皮革是物品制作中的理想原料。通过0级皮匠制作，可用于0-20级装备等用品制作。",en:"This skin still smells bad, but that doesn\'t stop it being a much sought-after resource in the crafting of shields."};
descriptions["2254"]={cn:"黄色羽毛，可爱小巧。用它来挠你朋友或者敌人的脚底。",en:"A cute yellow feather. Tickle your friends for pleasure or your enemies for torture."};
descriptions["2271"]={cn:"木板是物品制作中的理想原料。通过0级伐木制作，可用于0-20级装备等用品制作。",en:"A tree reduced to two dimensions... A plank."};
descriptions["2279"]={cn:"面粉是物品制作中的理想原料。通过0级种植制作，可用于0-20级装备等用品制作。",en:"You\'ll knead this flower to make bread and cakes."};
descriptions["2281"]={cn:"来自远古的尘埃，效力惊人。能让一切事物迅速衰老。很神奇吧！",en:"This powder might come from the Dofus Era, and its effects are surprising. It instantly ages anything it\'s mixed with. Magic, right?"};
descriptions["2292"]={cn:"镰刀手和纸张的边缘一样锋利。你甚至能用它们来收割小麦。",en:"This scythe\'s handle is about as sturdy as a piece of paper. You should just about manage to harvest some Wheat with it."};
descriptions["2293"]={cn:"宝藏猎人的谚语总是言简意赅...比如“出门挖宝的时候记得要带锄头”，说得太对了。",en:"Enutrof expressions have a unique simplicity... for example \'Make sure you bring a pick with you when you go digging.\' Simple but true. Oh so true."};
descriptions["2294"]={cn:"啾啾为了这顶帽子献出了生命。不用太内疚，是养殖的。",en:"Piwis were not only hurt, they were killed to make this human-scale representation of a Piwi\'s noggin."};
descriptions["2295"]={cn:"啾啾为了这顶帽子献出了生命。不用太内疚，是养殖的。",en:"Piwis were not only hurt, they were killed to make this human-scale representation of a Piwi\'s noggin."};
descriptions["2296"]={cn:"啾啾为了这顶帽子献出了生命。不用太内疚，是养殖的。",en:"Piwis were not only hurt, they were killed to make this human-scale representation of a Piwi\'s noggin."};
descriptions["2297"]={cn:"啾啾为了这顶帽子献出了生命。不用太内疚，是养殖的。",en:"Piwis were not only hurt, they were killed to make this human-scale representation of a Piwi\'s noggin."};
descriptions["2298"]={cn:"轻若无物的披风。事实上，它和啾啾大脑一样轻！",en:"This cloak is light, very light. In fact, it weighs about the same as a Piwi brain!"};
descriptions["2299"]={cn:"轻若无物的披风。事实上，它和啾啾大脑一样轻！",en:"This cloak is light, very light. In fact, it weighs about the same as a Piwi brain!"};
descriptions["2300"]={cn:"轻若无物的披风。事实上，它和啾啾大脑一样轻！",en:"This cloak is light, very light. In fact, it weighs about the same as a Piwi brain!"};
descriptions["2301"]={cn:"轻若无物的披风。事实上，它和啾啾大脑一样轻！",en:"This cloak is light, very light. In fact, it weighs about the same as a Piwi brain!"};
descriptions["2306"]={cn:"以爱之名，倾心打造。以一簇鲜亮的羽毛点缀，魅力倍增。",en:"This belt was made with love. The tuft of plumes is just to add a touch of glamour."};
descriptions["2307"]={cn:"以爱之名，倾心打造。以一簇鲜亮的羽毛点缀，魅力倍增。",en:"This belt was made with love. The tuft of plumes is just to add a touch of glamour."};
descriptions["2308"]={cn:"以爱之名，倾心打造。以一簇鲜亮的羽毛点缀，魅力倍增。",en:"This belt was made with love. The tuft of plumes is just to add a touch of glamour."};
descriptions["2309"]={cn:"以爱之名，倾心打造。以一簇鲜亮的羽毛点缀，魅力倍增。",en:"This belt was made with love. The tuft of plumes is just to add a touch of glamour."};
descriptions["2310"]={cn:"靴子奇迹般地增大了数倍，足够让你穿上。现在你可以放心坐在树枝上了，小心，也许会压断树枝掉下来...",en:"These Piwi claws have somehow been mysteriously expanded to fit your feet. Now, you can sit on branches, if they\'ll hold your weight."};
descriptions["2311"]={cn:"靴子奇迹般地增大了数倍，足够让你穿上。现在你可以放心坐在树枝上了，小心，也许会压断树枝掉下来...",en:"These Piwi claws have somehow been mysteriously expanded to fit your feet. Now, you can sit on branches, if they\'ll hold your weight."};
descriptions["2312"]={cn:"靴子奇迹般地增大了数倍，足够让你穿上。现在你可以放心坐在树枝上了，小心，也许会压断树枝掉下来...",en:"These Piwi claws have somehow been mysteriously expanded to fit your feet. Now, you can sit on branches, if they\'ll hold your weight."};
descriptions["2313"]={cn:"靴子奇迹般地增大了数倍，足够让你穿上。现在你可以放心坐在树枝上了，小心，也许会压断树枝掉下来...",en:"These Piwi claws have somehow been mysteriously expanded to fit your feet. Now, you can sit on branches, if they\'ll hold your weight."};
descriptions["2337"]={cn:"[ADMIN] 米歇尔特别喜欢这个胸针。她自恋极了，无论在家里还是在工作，她总是情不自禁，她对于暴击率简直着了魔。",en:"[ADMIN] Lucy loved it. She adored it even. She couldn\'t stop herself. At home, at work, she couldn\'t stop doing it. She was completely and utterly nuts about crits!"};
descriptions["2340"]={cn:"纯天然绿色灌装，这种纯净，柔和的水会给你带来前所未有的微妙口感，要确保没有绵球或者其他什么东西在里面小便之类的...",en:"Harvested straight from nature, this pure, soft water will please even the most delicate of palates. Just make sure a Gobball hasn\'t peed in it, or worse..."};
descriptions["2355"]={cn:"神奇的粉末，有很多用途...可以在洒在咕咕的尾巴上，从而轻易抓住它们，也可以喷在你的左肩上，施展诡异的巫毒法术。当然也可以用作调味品。",en:"This magic powder has many uses... You can catch Piwis with it by placing a single grain on one of their tails or cast strange voodoo spells by tossing it over your left shoulder. Some people even use it to flavor their food. Imagine that!"};
descriptions["2357"]={cn:"永远不要告诉一只绵团她的奶有股怪味。既然你喝不下她的奶，她也容不下你...",en:"Hardy and strong of taste, Mimilk is rich in calcium and protein."};
descriptions["2379"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["2385"]={cn:"森林的气息环绕着你，适合用来掩盖萨迪达身上野性的味道。",en:"Its woodland scent follows you everywhere. It\'s very practical for covering up that wild odor certain Sadidas give off!"};
descriptions["2395"]={cn:"梅姆巴是一只不恐高的幸运猫...他认为他始终能安然脱险。然而有一天，他碰到一只饥饿的巨魔...",en:"Maimpa was an Ecaflip who wasn\'t afraid of heights... he thought he\'d always land on his feet. One day, he landed on a starving Trool..."};
descriptions["2396"]={cn:"传说可以保护穿戴者免受天气变化影响，当然，对于奥古之乱你可别指望它能有什么作为！",en:"According to some legends, this ring can protect its wearer from bad weather. Unfortunately, it can\'t protect you from Ogrest\'s Chaos!"};
descriptions["2397"]={cn:"巨大的帆状植物，经常被冒险者用作吊床，因此得名。",en:"This huge cot-shaped plant is often used by adventurers as a hammock, hence its name."};
descriptions["2400"]={cn:"夏威夷胸衣是时尚人士的必备选择，但它还有一个优点，它能让你的敌人向着反方向逃跑。",en:"This Hawaiian Shirt might be an easy target for the fashion police, but it does have one advantage: it will send your enemies running in the opposite direction."};
descriptions["2408"]={cn:"还不如鼠牙锋利，但是分量却不轻。",en:"About as sharp as a sack of wet mice, but just as heavy."};
descriptions["2504"]={cn:"有点扎手，但是外观十分迷人。对于消化系统也有所裨益。天啊，还有什么事情是蓝蓟不能做到的？",en:"The thistle stings a bit, but this aggressive side doesn\'t make it any less charming. They\'re also good for the digestive system. Is there anything they can\'t do?"};
descriptions["2571"]={cn:"没用了...",en:"No longer used..."};
descriptions["2603"]={cn:"这个袋子并不是什么特殊的东西，看起来很普通，打开它随便放点你想放的东西吧。",en:"This bag isn\'t very special, that much is obvious. However, all you have to do is put things in it and you can take them with you anywhere!"};
descriptions["2634"]={cn:"深受宝藏猎人欢迎。",en:"Popular with Enutrofs, the Tou\'pee cap also functions as a wig."};
descriptions["2643"]={cn:"这件肩甲的事说不尽、道不完...",en:"We could go on and on about these epaulettes..."};
descriptions["2673"]={cn:"看起来像是从林地里随意捡起的一根老树枝。但是用来自卫也绰绰有余了。",en:"It looks like an old piece of wood picked up off the forest floor, but it\'s strong enough for you to defend yourself with."};
descriptions["2675"]={cn:"构造简单的魔杖，普普通通。",en:"This is a very simple wand. Not the stuff of legends."};
descriptions["2676"]={cn:"谁想得到一只被自己的便便困住的豆芙能制造出一把坚硬的锤子？退一步讲，根本没人能想到他能做出锤子来。",en:"Who would have thought that a Tofu trapped in his own guano could make such a strong hammer? Who would have thought it could make a hammer at all?"};
descriptions["2682"]={cn:"粘稠的液体一滴滴掉下来，泛着淡淡的绿光。你开始后悔捡起来了...",en:"Slimy, dripping, tinged with greenish hues that make you think you would have done better to leave it on the ground..."};
descriptions["2698"]={cn:"十分小巧的蛋。吃下去的时候你发现咬到的全是蛋壳。",en:"Piwi Eggs are very small. So small that you\'d better get used to the taste of the shell if you ever want to get a meal!"};
descriptions["2702"]={cn:"无论用作衣帽架还是门楔，或者当做壁炉架上的装饰品，啾啾嘴都会让你看起来很没品味。",en:"Whether you use it as a coatrack or door wedge, or keep it as an ornament on your mantelpiece, this Piwi Beak will always be in very bad taste."};
descriptions["2709"]={cn:"点击两下来把整组古代资源转换成新的资源。古代资源需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["2731"]={cn:"用新鲜的羊炼乳烹制，宴会佳品！",en:"Cooked with fresh Gobbette cream, this thigh will be a real treat!"};
descriptions["2734"]={cn:"除掉豆芙的四肢之后，你的炖豆芙已经做好一半了！真棒！为孩子们做个可口的豆芙汉堡吧。",en:"Remove the legs of a Tofu and you get ready made meatballs! Voila! A delicious Tofu Burger for your children."};
descriptions["2822"]={cn:"没有比它更便宜的戒指了！",en:"Cheaper than this ring, there is not!"};
descriptions["2865"]={cn:"贪婪的冒险者争先恐后地来争抢这种美食。",en:"Greedy adventurers will be falling over each other for its delicately smoked taste."};
descriptions["2869"]={cn:"吞剑人伯里克利制造了这柄剑，用以保证他的喉咙滋润。不幸的是，他没有活到这柄剑派上用处的那一天。",en:"Perryclees, the sword swallower, made this sword to keep his breath fresh at all times. Unfortunately, he didn\'t live long enough to see if it worked."};
descriptions["2895"]={cn:"[ADMIN] 这种作弊用的东西，有什么好描述的呢！（蕾顿：反正也没人会看的啊。）",en:"[ADMIN] It\'s hard to take admin item descriptions seriously, actually! \n(Author\'s note: Es dificil de taker descriptions items admin serioso, actuallé.)"};
descriptions["2957"]={cn:"帮助西卡·英格拉斯熬过了无数次绵球军的背叛。",en:"This amulet has allowed Shika Ingalsse to survive numerous Gobball rebellions."};
descriptions["2960"]={cn:"实际上只是一块糖果。在你把它塞进嘴巴之前，你要知道它曾经被共计36代女兽人的胳肢窝蹂躏过。",en:"This amulet is, in fact, a piece of candy. Before you go putting it in your mouth, though, you might like to know that it was made by being rolled under the armpits of 36 generations of female Bworks in heat."};
descriptions["2986"]={cn:"由在一桶啤酒中浸泡了5000年的月亮石制成。它威力十足。",en:"The Gougnole is made from the moon stone, which had been soaking in a barrel of root beer for 5000 years. As a result, it\'s awfully powerful."};
descriptions["2990"]={cn:"纯木制成。伐木工认为它能完成不可能的任务。",en:"This amulet, made exclusively of wood, is prized by lumberjacks who think it can do things it couldn\'t possibly do."};
descriptions["3018"]={cn:"小巧精致。",en:"This ring makes the finger wearing it much smaller and daintier."};
descriptions["3026"]={cn:"虽然它不值分文，阿玛克纳收藏家会为了这个戒指抢破脑袋。",en:"Amaknian collectors would and do kill for this ring, though it isn\'t worth a brass farthing."};
descriptions["3332"]={cn:"传说艾卡菲利在成神前使用的武器。它由艾卡菲利的九条尾巴中的一条制成。",en:"Legend has it that Ecaflip, during the terrible fight that raised him to the rank of god, used a weapon made out of the tails from each of his nine lives."};
descriptions["3474"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["3565"]={cn:"削尖之后是一件强大的武器，用来搔敌人的脚底板再好不过了。",en:"When correctly sharpened, a Rat Moustache can be a formidable weapon, ideal for tickling your enemies\' feet."};
descriptions["3566"]={cn:"可以用来制成鞭子或者腰带...能用就好！",en:"You can use this rat tail to make a whip or a belt... it doesn\'t matter as long as you find something to do with it!"};
descriptions["3574"]={cn:"为什么要捡起来？实在太恶心了！",en:"But...  but...  what made you pick it up? It\'s disgusting!"};
descriptions["3599"]={cn:"挥舞着这柄大斧，你仿佛变成了“意见领袖”。如果有人和你意见不一致，喷死他。来，战至灰烬吧！",en:"Wield this axe and you will immediately feel like a true \'leader of troops\'. If opinion on this is divided, let it fall upon the heads of the unruly. At least you\'ll be the only one left with any say."};
descriptions["3601"]={cn:"制造这把弓的匠人，马弓·藏哀，也不知道如何使用它。他打败敌人的同时，也弄伤自己。",en:"The man who created this bow, a certain Marc Hidsad, never really knew how to use it. He usually hurt himself just as much as his enemies."};
descriptions["3608"]={cn:"制造这件披风只有一个目的：它必须连着数天都能让主人清醒着。",en:"This cape was made with just one goal in mind: It had to be able to keep its owner awake for a few days running."};
descriptions["3663"]={cn:"嗯嗯...新鲜的菊芋片，用榛子油浸泡过。你觉得饿了，对吗？",en:"Hmm...  freshly peeled Artichokes immersed in Hazelnut oil. It makes you hungry, no? How does it not?"};
descriptions["3745"]={cn:"闪亮松脆的蜘蛛腿为美食家的餐桌增色不少。害怕蜘蛛的人还是老实点吃牛蛙腿的好。",en:"Light and crisp, these Arachnee legs delight the palate of experimental cuisine lovers. Arachneephobes better stick to frogs\' legs."};
descriptions["3752"]={cn:"蜘蛛丝的粘度足以修复任何损坏的物品...只要你能用手把它们分开。",en:"Arachnee Silk is so sticky that it will repair any broken object... As soon as you\'ve managed to unstick your hands."};
descriptions["3753"]={cn:"据说蜘蛛腿能带来好运。如果不起作用的话，就直接吃掉它们。作为开胃菜十分可口。",en:"It is said that Arachnee legs bring luck. If that doesn\'t work, you can always eat them. They are delicious roasted as a starter!"};
descriptions["3812"]={cn:"为了保证触感更舒适，卡牌的边缘镶上了羊毛，骚气熏人。",en:"To guarantee a more comfortable grip, the edges of these cards have been covered with Gobball wool. It\'s sweet, but unbelievably smelly."};
descriptions["3823"]={cn:"为猎鸟人专门打造。轻便易用，擅于攻击敌人的弱点。",en:"This bow was specially created for bird hunting. Light and easy to handle, it\'s useful for ruffling almost anyone\'s feathers."};
descriptions["3827"]={cn:"毫无疑问，这柄法杖能毁坏一切！无论是骷髅、软骨，还是其他任何东西都不堪一击！聆听敌人骨头粉碎的美妙音乐吧...",en:"There are no two ways about it, this staff crushes everything! Skull, cartilage, everything! That will be music to the ears of those you who like the sound of bones cracking..."};
descriptions["3833"]={cn:"被幸运猫姑娘们用来惩罚出轨的情人...割掉身体的一部分...一定是手，我确定。",en:"The female Ecaflips use these cards to avenge the infidelity of their partner... by cutting off a body part...  the hands, I\'m sure."};
descriptions["3836"]={cn:"激进的匕首，如果你和它有摩擦，它立刻就会背叛你！",en:"This dagger is so aggressive that if you contradict it, it may turn against you!"};
descriptions["3849"]={cn:"你又没管住自己的手...又一把毛用没有的剑！别再说这是最后一把剑了，没人相信你！",en:"Once again you failed to control your urge... Another sword you\'ll never use! Stop saying that this is the last: No one believes you!"};
descriptions["3864"]={cn:"如果你喜欢既能填饱肚子也兼顾营养均衡的菜肴...那么豆芙团子不该是你的选择！",en:"If you love filling yet balanced dishes...you should know that the Tofu Dumpling is not for you!"};
descriptions["3886"]={cn:"这个匕首对于止疼有着惊人的效果，非常适合那些不想听到他们对手哭泣的人佩戴，那些觉得它很有趣的家伙们实在太坏了。",en:"This dagger has the specific property of preventing pain. Ideal for those who hate to hear their opponents cry. Too bad for those who find it amusing."};
descriptions["3895"]={cn:"小贴士：不可食用！",en:"Here\'s some friendly advice: don\'t eat it! Not that it looks particularly appetizing anyway..."};
descriptions["3896"]={cn:"你值得拥有。",en:"Because you\'re worth it."};
descriptions["3898"]={cn:"植物残渣装成一瓶。真美味！",en:"Field Plant spit now comes in bottles. Yummy!"};
descriptions["3903"]={cn:"别搞错了：并不是因为牙齿不健康而导致牙齿呈金黄色，而是因为他们喜欢亮闪闪的东西。",en:"Make no mistake: Cracklers don\'t have gold teeth because of poor dental hygiene, but because they love their bling."};
descriptions["3920"]={cn:"这个袋子只是个普通的不能再普通的袋子，打开它随便放点你想放的东西吧。",en:"There\'s nothing very special about this bag. However, all you have to do is put things in it and you can take them with you anywhere!"};
descriptions["3924"]={cn:"弓就是你的生命。敌人会无情地执行命令...现在轮到你了...",en:"Now that you have it, it\'s the most important thing in your life. Your enemies will not hesitate to obey their master - now you call the shots..."};
descriptions["3941"]={cn:"刻在木头上的漂亮卡牌，足够让豆芙在恐惧中颤抖！",en:"Beautiful cards engraved in wood, enough to make a Tofu tremble in fear!"};
descriptions["3945"]={cn:"不停地挠主人的手心，让无聊的冒险者在战斗中享受额外乐趣。",en:"This clock hand has the annoying tendency of tickling its bearer\'s hand, which adds an extra element of challenge in battle for the more blasé adventurer."};
descriptions["3953"]={cn:"专挑年轻的勇士下手...",en:"A hammer that preys on the youngest warriors..."};
descriptions["3959"]={cn:"镶铁的手杖，雕刻着绵球图案。用来击打别人的时候，你会听到一声响亮的“哎呦”！",en:"This steel rimmed staff with its Gobball carving really commands respect. When you use it to hit someone, the only noise to break the revered silence will be \"Ow\"!"};
descriptions["3974"]={cn:"不放心自己辛辛苦苦挣来的卡玛的人有福了。有了此盾，他们大可安心。",en:"This is great for those who want to look after their hard-earned kamas. Finally, a shield made for the well-off!"};
descriptions["3976"]={cn:"由酒馆招牌制成的护盾，能保证你不头痛，大概是这样...恩，没错的。",en:"This shield, made from a tavern sign, will make sure you don\'t get any headaches, but that\'s about it."};
descriptions["3988"]={cn:"轮廓硬朗的钻戒。毫无疑问，敌人的注意力会被你吸引过来...",en:"The shape of this ring is pretty explicit. Your enemies will pay attention to you, make no bones about it..."};
descriptions["4033"]={cn:"轻轻一击，就可以灭绝天行者一家。",en:"Just one stroke of this sword on a target, and a blink of its eye, will trigger the apocalypse for all its brothers and sisters surrounding it."};
descriptions["4040"]={cn:"爱炫耀的人都喜欢，是十二世界中最精华的部分。",en:"The show-off\'s dream, these wands are the cream of the crop in the World of Twelve."};
descriptions["4068"]={cn:"[ADMIN] 你可以将任意物品放进这个袋子里。特别是杰夫那里抢来的装备。",en:"[ADMIN] This bag will let you keep all sorts of items in it. It particularly likes it when you furnish it with items nicked from other adventurers."};
descriptions["4141"]={cn:"这双靴子（或者说靴子的臭气）制造时曾受过一位知名模特的启发。穿上之后你会觉得对自己充满自信，比以前动作更快，也更坚强。",en:"These boots (or their odor, at least) were inspired by a famous model. Put them on and you\'ll feel so sure of yourself that you\'ll actually be faster and more resistant than before."};
descriptions["4144"]={cn:"如果队友快没气了，这块盾可以救他一命！随便挥挥，即刻起效。",en:"If your allies start getting out of breath, this shield can be a real lifesaver! Just wave it vigorously in all directions."};
descriptions["4145"]={cn:"听起来很厉害的样子。新手用不错。",en:"No, this item isn\'t any better than its name implies. We all have to start somewhere though, right?"};
descriptions["4146"]={cn:"这只树皮覆盖的戒指将成为你的战斗利器。",en:"This bark-covered ring will help you take revenge on your enemies."};
descriptions["4150"]={cn:"为你的胸部提供特殊保护。别担心，即便是男人也能提供很好的保护。",en:"A breastplate gives you optimal support in the chest department for that special va va voom effect. Don\'t worry, if you\'re a man, it works equally well on your moobs."};
descriptions["4161"]={cn:"这件披风散发着一股刺鼻的气味。其实只是多种怪物毛皮的混合物而已。",en:"Fair enough, this cloak has a very strong and unpleasant odor. It\'s basically a mix of various monster furs."};
descriptions["4164"]={cn:"看上去普普通通，不值什么钱。但是一旦破产，你会巴不得卖了它。前提是你能找到买家。",en:"This ring doesn\'t look like much, but you\'ll be glad to have the option to sell it if you ever go bust! If you manage to find a buyer, that is!"};
descriptions["4165"]={cn:"赫莉是一位伊欧普的信徒。她立志扫平四方恶魔。她从不乱发脾气，除非有人以为她是胆小鬼。",en:"Holly was a Iop disciple who had sworn to strike down evil wherever she went. She never lost her temper, except when people compared her to a certain Oly."};
descriptions["4179"]={cn:"比糖还甜，但是十分耐用。",en:"Sweeter than the Mutton Candy, but just as durable."};
descriptions["4181"]={cn:"点击两下来把整组古代资源转换成新的资源。古代资源需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["4183"]={cn:"点击两下来把整组古代资源转换成新的资源。古代资源需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["4192"]={cn:"不要和同品牌的东西混淆了。",en:"Not to be confused with the bra of the same name from the \"Lovely Chassis\" series by Jean-Trool Grospied."};
descriptions["4205"]={cn:"只有一条忠告：别穿！",en:"The only inspiring thing about this is the idea of never wearing it."};
descriptions["4207"]={cn:"即便你像龙成一样飞檐走壁，也抖不掉这件轻盈的披风。",en:"This cloak is so liquid and light it will hang on to your back through all your Chackie Jan moments"};
descriptions["4208"]={cn:"曾经属于战争领主斯特拉克尔大帝的披风。他拥有出色的战略才能，迫不及待地想要征服世界。",en:"This superb cloak once belonged to the Great Stratequerre, the warlord renowned for his expert strategy and hunger for the conquest of the universe."};
descriptions["4218"]={cn:"由奥金纳克残骸以及其他残渣制成。因为长期由恐怖的古尔洛拥有，道奇成为了荒凉的象征。",en:"The Daudgee is made from Ouginak remains and various other refuse. Worn by Gourlo the Terrible for a long time, the Daudgee is the image of desolation."};
descriptions["4220"]={cn:"为饥渴的矿工准备。",en:"For miners who are hungry for ore."};
descriptions["4224"]={cn:"华丽的皮革头盔，曾经属于尤伊克·克朗普，祖尔格的表兄。他们都十分喜欢紧身皮衣。",en:"This magnificent leather mask once belonged to Jouik Krampe, cousin of Zeurg. They were both fond of tight leather clothes."};
descriptions["4226"]={cn:"如果你拥有一个伐木工之魂并且深爱着大大的木结，那么这个腰带正好适合你，当然它也可能是你的不幸。",en:"If you have the soul of a lumberjack and you love big knots, this belt\'s for you. It may well be your undoing, however."};
descriptions["4229"]={cn:"是的，你没看错。唯一帮你提起裤子的东西，就是从腰带里渗出的粘稠液体。",en:"No, you\'re not going mad. The only thing holding your trousers up is, indeed, this viscous and sticky liquid dripping from your belt."};
descriptions["4230"]={cn:"土匪们增加了他们腰包的空间，以免抢劫的时候装不下。",en:"The Riktus have reinforced the purse attachment to make sure they don\'t get beaten at their own game."};
descriptions["4237"]={cn:"这条腰带有很多不同的传说，但是所有人都知道那是瞎说！",en:"There are plenty of theories about the conception of this belt, but everyone knows they\'re all pipe dreams!"};
descriptions["4240"]={cn:"唤醒你内心的野兽。",en:"These epaulettes will awaken the sleeping beast inside of you."};
descriptions["4248"]={cn:"黏糊糊的护肩，让人恶心。就算是你老妈也不愿意拥抱你。",en:"These epaulettes are so slimy and disgusting that even your own mother won\'t want to give you a hug."};
descriptions["4251"]={cn:"外形看起来好像你随身携带的钱包。当你输掉战斗的时候，可以装作你勇敢战斗过的样子。",en:"These epaulettes shaped like a purse will carry your makeup everywhere you go. Very helpful for putting on a brave face when you lose."};
descriptions["4262"]={cn:"商业庇护宝石：为热爱做生意，同时也会审时度势的冒险者精心准备。",en:"The Merchant Haven-Gem: For adventurers who have trading in the blood, but jelly in the knees!"};
descriptions["4263"]={cn:"这个庇护宝石会给你一个有着质朴地板的房间。无法要求更有神秘感的装饰，而你的信誉肯定会提高。",en:"This haven-gem will give you a room with rustic flooring. You couldn\'t ask for a more mysterious interior, and your credibility is sure to go up."};
descriptions["4264"]={cn:"厌倦了四处寻找工作台？有了制造庇护宝石，你就有了一个真正的专业工作室！",en:"Tired of running around looking for somewhere to work? With the crafting haven-gem, you\'ll get a true professional workshop!"};
descriptions["4266"]={cn:"纵观历史，魔术师总是能从帽子里掏出疯兔。有了这枚宝石，他们可以从口袋里掏出萝卜了！",en:"Throughout history, magicians have been able to mysteriously pull Wabbits out of their hat. With this Haven-Gem, they can now pull Cawwots out of their bag!"};
descriptions["4273"]={cn:"看起来普普通通，但是能孕育出典雅的金雀花朵。",en:"This seed doesn\'t look like much, but it\'ll give birth to a beautiful Gorsegoyle."};
descriptions["4275"]={cn:"现在是一颗种子，未来是一片蓝蓟花田。你只需要把它种在养分充足的地方就可以了，比如说敌人的裤裆里...",en:"From this seed, many thistles could be born. Simply plant it in fertile soil, such as an enemy\'s underpants..."};
descriptions["4278"]={cn:"总有人把麦秸当做最后的稻草。",en:"Once they\'ve harvest their wheat, some farmers find themselves clutching at straws."};
descriptions["4279"]={cn:"用于编织篮子，篮子里可以用来放大麦茶。大麦真有用！",en:"Barley Straws are used to make baskets...  in which you can carry drinks concocted from barley grains..."};
descriptions["4280"]={cn:"为双腿修长的自恋渔夫设计。",en:"Boots made for fishermen who have beautiful legs and know it."};
descriptions["4282"]={cn:"圣波翠克靴子",en:"Saint Potrick Boots"};
descriptions["4313"]={cn:"能有效防护朝向胸口的重击...副作用是让你呼吸困难。",en:"This armored breastplate prevents fatal blows to the chest...  that and breathing."};
descriptions["4314"]={cn:"袒露内心真实的自己。",en:"A breastplate for those who want to reveal the animal within."};
descriptions["4321"]={cn:"肯定是他。那两条鲜黄的肩带就是最好证据。",en:"It\'s most definitely him. You can tell by the two straps, yellower than a lemon."};
descriptions["4326"]={cn:"曾属于一名幸运猫，但是他喜欢赤脚走路，所以他只穿了一次，以后再也没穿过。",en:"Originally these were offered to an Ecaflip, but he liked walking barefoot so much he spent the rest of his life refusing them."};
descriptions["4327"]={cn:"远看近看都像是一双经典款式的兽人靴。",en:"From a distance, these look like classic Bwork boots. And from close up, too."};
descriptions["4328"]={cn:"专为因身高问题而烦恼的冒险家而设计。",en:"A pair of boots made for adventurers who think that size matters."};
descriptions["4335"]={cn:"如此可爱的种子怎么会变成丑陋的蔬菜？你现在可以体会你的父母是怎么想的了...",en:"How can such pretty seeds give rise to such an ugly vegetable? You now understand how your parents feel..."};
descriptions["4336"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["4346"]={cn:"方便小巧，是庇护袋的标准配置。不过要是想建立起一个商业帝国，你还有很长的路要走。",en:"A window that comes standard with your Haven Bag. It\'s convenient, but you\'re going to need more than that to build a business empire!"};
descriptions["4353"]={cn:"对于那些消耗起来无节制的人，这是个理想的货架！",en:"The ideal showcase for all those who consume without moderation!"};
descriptions["4440"]={cn:"种下一颗亚麻种子，就是拯救了一朵小花。",en:"Every flax seed planted is a little flower saved."};
descriptions["4441"]={cn:"这朵花虽轻，但比你预想的更加不屈不挠、坚韧不拔。",en:"This flower is so light you\'ll have a hard time believing just how rigid and resistant it is."};
descriptions["4442"]={cn:"萨迪达父母经常吓唬小孩子，说如果吃了一颗芦苇种子，芦苇会在你肚子里生根发芽，最终从你耳朵里长出来。",en:"Sadida parents tell their children that if you eat one of these, a reed will grow in your stomach and come out of your ears."};
descriptions["4443"]={cn:"柯龙宗师经常说『芦苇百弯不折』。但是出于安全考虑，这位熊猫武僧还是喜欢用更为结实的竹棍。",en:"Master Kano always said: \"The Reed may bend, but it never breaks\". Pandawas prefer to use a strong bamboo stick, just to be on the safe side."};
descriptions["4444"]={cn:"如果找到了这种珍稀的种子，你会交好运的。或者，你有这方面天分。",en:"If you manage to get your hands on this rare seed, you must be lucky. That or you have flair!"};
descriptions["4455"]={cn:"点击两下来把整组古代资源转换成新的符文粉末。古代资源需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["4502"]={cn:"只有幽灵才能制造出这么奇怪的物质。好吧，也有可能是一只发情的绵团...",en:"Only Ghostofs can produce a substance as strange as this. Well, either them or a Gobblette in heat..."};
descriptions["4524"]={cn:"摩擦树精的树干几分钟后你就可以得到这种精华，它的作用主要是用来制备止咳糖浆。",en:"Rub the trunk of a Treechnid for a few minutes and you get this sap, mainly used in the preparation of throat syrup."};
descriptions["4527"]={cn:"当这双靴子穿在你的脚上的时候，你将会感到...你靴子上有你的脚趾。",en:"With these boots round your toes, you\'ll feel...  like you have your toes in boots."};
descriptions["4528"]={cn:"倒过来放就可以用作水果篮子，又或者是沿街乞讨的容器。现代科技真先进。",en:"Turned upside down, this straw hat can be used as a fruit basket or a container for begging in the street. Isn\'t modern technology wonderful?"};
descriptions["4535"]={cn:"这是一个旧的包包。最好的办法是摆脱它，得到一个新的袋子！",en:"This bag is an old version. The best thing to do is to get rid of it and get a new bag!"};
descriptions["4592"]={cn:"魔法卷轴，神秘的钥匙...很多迷人的小物件都能放在上面。真是一件代表了科研奇迹和最新技术的发明！",en:"This display can contain quite fascinating objects: magic scrolls, mysterious keys... A real little miracle of ingenuity and the latest technology!"};
descriptions["4606"]={cn:"测试戒指等级 05",en:"Test ring lvl 5"};
descriptions["4607"]={cn:"测试戒指等级 10",en:"Test ring lvl 10"};
descriptions["4608"]={cn:"测试戒指等级 15",en:"Test ring lvl 15"};
descriptions["4609"]={cn:"测试戒指等级 20",en:"Test ring lvl 20"};
descriptions["4610"]={cn:"测试戒指等级 25",en:"Test ring lvl 25"};
descriptions["4611"]={cn:"测试戒指等级 30",en:"Test ring lvl 30"};
descriptions["4612"]={cn:"测试戒指等级 35",en:"Test ring lvl 35"};
descriptions["4613"]={cn:"测试戒指等级 40",en:"Test ring lvl 40"};
descriptions["4615"]={cn:"无情地攻击敌人的弱点。",en:"This clock hand can burrow its own way into your enemy\'s orifices."};
descriptions["4838"]={cn:"如果你做了卑鄙下流的事，这只背包会离开你。",en:"This bag will rebel if you try to do something it considers vile or nasty."};
descriptions["4985"]={cn:"由刺蓟纤维制成。小心手指：戒指上有很多刺...",en:"A ring made from woven Thistle fibers. Be careful with your fingers: it\'s probably full of thorns..."};
descriptions["4988"]={cn:"把蓝蓟和荨麻编织在一起，效果完美！再挑剔的受虐狂也会喜欢的！",en:"Thistle and Nettle fibers woven together, and what an effect! Even the most demanding of Osas will love it!"};
descriptions["5002"]={cn:"新手向前冲！",en:"GoGo Xp n00b!"};
descriptions["5010"]={cn:"味道好极了...好吧吗，起码能喝下去...呃，我得承认实际上很恶心。",en:"Thistle Broth is good. Well... edible, that is. Ok, it\'s disgusting."};
descriptions["5046"]={cn:"只有为了崇高理想而战斗的冒险者才配得上这双靴子。宝剑赠英雄，名靴送骑士。",en:"Only adventurers fighting for noble causes are deemed worthy to wear these boots. That said, they do look pretty good on you..."};
descriptions["5055"]={cn:"砰！",en:"The ID of the item and its category are used in the code. Do not remove or change items\' categories."};
descriptions["5066"]={cn:"砰！",en:"The ID of the item and its category are used in the code. Do not remove or change items\' categories."};
descriptions["5071"]={cn:"砰！",en:"The ID of the item and its category are used in the code. Do not remove or change items\' categories."};
descriptions["5169"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["5197"]={cn:"治愈者主妇参与女权运动时的武器，擦拭灰尘的同时也可以打打怪。多实用啊！",en:"This wand is behind the emancipation of Eniripsa housewives. It\'s excellent for getting rid of both monsters and dust. Practical, no?"};
descriptions["5309"]={cn:"柔软、崭新、干净...哦抱歉，一点也不干净。",en:"It\'s soft, it\'s new, and it\'s clean... Oh sorry, it\'s not clean."};
descriptions["5310"]={cn:"仅仅靠刺鼻的臭气就可以躲过毁灭的命运。",en:"The first woolen shoulder pads that can kill...  annihilation by odor, that is."};
descriptions["5311"]={cn:"难道没人告诉你黄色特别适合你吗？是的？令人惊讶的...",en:"Have you ever been told that yellow suits you? Yes? Amazing..."};
descriptions["5407"]={cn:"从前，女宝藏猎人将变异虫壳敷在脸上，皱纹很快就消失了。眼睛鼻子嘴巴也没了...",en:"In times gone by, lady Enutrofs used to apply dried larva skin to their faces. Within seconds, their wrinkles disappeared. Along with the rest of it..."};
descriptions["5409"]={cn:"啦啦啦，啦啦啦...香蕉！哇哦哦哦！",en:"Na na na na, Na na na... Citronana! Whoooo!"};
descriptions["5410"]={cn:"幸福膏，幸福膏！吃过都说好，一口百病消，两口万事顺，三口赛神仙！",en:"Euphoric resin! If you eat it, it\'ll really make your head spin!"};
descriptions["5411"]={cn:"总有捣蛋鬼喜欢戴上它来吓唬其他游泳的人。真好玩...当然，当他被海怪当做是活鱼的时候就不好玩了。",en:"Some practical jokers stick this thing on their back to scare the bathers. What fun... until they get mistaken for helpless fish by the local sea monster, that is."};
descriptions["5412"]={cn:"一只死去的旋鸟和一只死去的豆芙很相似，有时候很容易混淆。",en:"It is disturbing how similar a dead Whirly and a dead Tofu are!"};
descriptions["5413"]={cn:"我们都知道旋鸟们满载着炙热的气体，现在枯木旋鸟的精华让我们知道了它的存在。",en:"We knew that Whirlies were full of hot air. Now the Whirlitsar\'s sappy and we know it."};
descriptions["5426"]={cn:"轻便弹性好。",en:"Pooplar Wood is light and bendy."};
descriptions["5433"]={cn:"你得知道所有的猎人都是靠猎物的价值养家糊口的。这根羽毛毫无疑问是值钱的。",en:"Know that every hunter thrives at the expense of the creature he murders. This lesson is well worth a feather, no doubt."};
descriptions["5434"]={cn:"乌鸦也许是最聪明的鸟类，十分重视胎教...",en:"Crobaks in the fields, feed, feed, Crobaks in the fields, feed their babies..."};
descriptions["5436"]={cn:"点击两下来把整组古代资源转换成新的资源。古代资源需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["5437"]={cn:"原来你喜欢贝利。",en:"So you too like all that tom peckery after all."};
descriptions["5438"]={cn:"有了这个酸性的爪子，你在也不用担心你会抓不住你的敌人！",en:"With this acidic claw, you won\'t have to worry about losing your grip on your enemies!"};
descriptions["5439"]={cn:"乌鸦内脏肉质结实，口感丰富。为了能保证充分享受美食，千万不要去想乌鸦生前吃了些什么。",en:"These Crow innards are firm and rich in taste. To appreciate the flavor fully, avoid thinking about all the filth the animal has swallowed in its lifetime."};
descriptions["5440"]={cn:"又香又软，三倍厚度...随身携带以防不测。传统的冬青叶子可以淘汰了。",en:"The leaves of this clover are soft and scented, of triple thickness...  just in case you need such a thing. Ideal replacement for Ivy leaves."};
descriptions["5443"]={cn:"玉米香脆可口、口味甘甜，所以大家都爱吃。",en:"Everyone loves corn, with its characteristic crunch and naturally sweet taste!"};
descriptions["5444"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["5445"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["5446"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["5447"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["5449"]={cn:"现在你找到了碎石者铁石心肠的证据！",en:"Now you have proof that Cracklers have a heart of stone!"};
descriptions["5453"]={cn:"极易生长，随处可见。",en:"Even a total scruffball can plant them."};
descriptions["5461"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["5462"]={cn:"用于掩盖油光光的头发，也可用作纸巾。\n狂战士专用。",en:"This bandana is great for camouflaging a greasy mane of hair, and it can also be used as a tissue."};
descriptions["5468"]={cn:"就算是勇士斯帕达，当年也没机会戴上这顶头盔。上面的宝石和铁板足够保证你的小脑袋安然无恙。",en:"Even Spartapine, the Great Reaper, never had the chance to wear a helmet like this. The precious stones and metals used to make it ensure your noggin will be kept safe and sound inside."};
descriptions["5474"]={cn:"稀有的矿石。挖掘含有铅矿的土壤，充分洗净，然后整块融化。接下来你可以取消所有的约会了...",en:"This ore is not easy to mine. Recover clods of soil with traces of lead ore, rinse copiously, and then melt the whole lot. Phew, you better start cancelling appointments..."};
descriptions["5491"]={cn:"穿上这件外套，你再也不用怕宝藏猎人了。他们害怕乌龟！",en:"With this armor on your back, you\'re safe from Enutrofs. They\'re afraid of turtles, they are!"};
descriptions["5508"]={cn:"谁能想得到有一天你也用得到猪鬃？",en:"Who would have thought that one day the fleece of a big hairy pig might interest you?"};
descriptions["5510"]={cn:"爱鱿在它们受到惊吓的时候会喷出墨水。它们开心和生气的时候也会喷墨水。其实你随时都会被淋一身。",en:"Kraloves shoot ink when frightened. Or happy. Or angry. In other words, it\'s not that hard to come by."};
descriptions["5513"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["5515"]={cn:"宝藏猎人看到你有这块皮会嫉妒得眼红的。",en:"This fur will be the envy of all the Enutrofettes for miles around. Don\'t wear in the presence of Rigide Barjo."};
descriptions["5518"]={cn:"如果有人胆敢骚扰你，不要犹豫亮出你的獠牙！",en:"If someone comes to bother you, don\'t hesitate to bare your fangs! Just the trick..."};
descriptions["5521"]={cn:"它会夹人？只要不夹我就好。",en:"Does it snip or pinch? As long as it doesn\'t clip, it\'s okay by me."};
descriptions["5524"]={cn:"蟹肉始终是盘中美食。不要再单纯地认为螃蟹是无足轻重的食腐动物了。",en:"Cwab Meat is always a delight to the palate. To appreciate its true value, don\'t think about the fact that the creature is an indiscriminate scavenger."};
descriptions["5528"]={cn:"这块布确实很吓人。你已经拿在手上看了？快害怕呀，丢掉，丢掉...",en:"This cloth is truly appalling. Now that you have it in your hands, you\'re probably wondering what led you to pick it up..."};
descriptions["5529"]={cn:"如果稻草人全体决定宣布独立的话，世上就没有秸秆了。",en:"If all the scarecrows decided to assert their independence, that really would be the last straw!"};
descriptions["5545"]={cn:"见鬼...一枚光光的戒指！",en:"What the... This ring is naked!"};
descriptions["5568"]={cn:"这棵树根是树精有脚气的良好佐证。",en:"This piece of wood is the foul-smelling irrefutable proof that Treechnids have foot-odor issues!"};
descriptions["5569"]={cn:"从树灵脂化石中提炼而成。看起来像一个巨大的绵球血块。",en:"From fossilized Treechnid sap. Something like a large Gobball blood clot, in fact."};
descriptions["5580"]={cn:"洪水激发了这柄剑的潜能。它从水中吸取了新的复仇力量。",en:"The flood seems to have been hugely beneficial to this blessed sword, which has drawn a new and vengeful power from the water."};
descriptions["5666"]={cn:"这把古怪的弓是为一个小村庄里固步自封的国王专门打造的。他十分喜欢同时发出两只箭矢来炫耀威力。",en:"This unconventional bow was designed specifically for the self-proclaimed king of a village of peasants, who loved showing off by firing two arrows simultaneously."};
descriptions["5690"]={cn:"奥兹是一名来自南极的魔术师，经常向人们诉说着一个没脑子的稻草人的故事。很显然，没脑子并不意味着缺心眼。",en:"Oz, a magician from the South Pole, often told the story of a scarecrow without a brain. Obviously, the lack of a brain doesn\'t mean you don\'t have a heart."};
descriptions["5886"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["5899"]={cn:"能让周围的人群大笑。笑你，不是和你一起笑。",en:"The Truffle Shovel will make the people around you laugh. At you, though, not with you."};
descriptions["5928"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["5945"]={cn:"看看吧！一只巨大的海星爱上了你的盾牌！",en:"Would you look at that! This huge star has taken a liking to your shield!"};
descriptions["5963"]={cn:"这斗篷是用红胡子制作的...很特别。斗篷被极强的魔法赋予了生命，特别喜欢向穿戴着它的那些可怜虫搞恶作剧。",en:"This cloak is made of red beard hair... it is quite unique. Animated by extraordinarily powerful magic that renders it all but living, it adores playing practical jokes on the unfortunate soul who puts it on."};
descriptions["5971"]={cn:"是的，狼也需要带头绳，你问这是为什么？所有人都需要展示他温柔的一面不是吗！",en:"Yes, Boowolwes also wear Strings, so what? Everyone is entitled to their share of femininity!"};
descriptions["5993"]={cn:"勿空一口气吃了太多的仙豆。他系紧了这条腰带，放了个响屁，然后坐上了那朵著名的云彩。",en:"When Sangroku had eaten too many magic beans, he tied this belt hard around his waist to plug the winds of panic for which he was famous."};
descriptions["5994"]={cn:"用约翰的短裤碎片制成。足以让酒吧里的漂亮女海盗们脸红心跳。",en:"This belt has been made out of LeChouque\'s most powerful belongings: in particular, his famous boxer shorts. It\'s enough to plunge the entire female clientele of the Pirates Bar into mass confusion."};
descriptions["6029"]={cn:"测试戒指等级 50",en:"Test ring lvl 50"};
descriptions["6121"]={cn:"由凝固的绵球污垢制成的武器。十分强大的武器。",en:"A sword made from solidified Gobball grime. In other words, a formidable weapon."};
descriptions["6162"]={cn:"为木头上光的最佳机会。",en:"There\'s never been such a good opportunity to polish your wood."};
descriptions["6219"]={cn:"测试戒指等级 70 （一个就够了！）",en:"Test ring lvl 70 (one\'s enough!)"};
descriptions["6220"]={cn:"其实就是一块石头...但是如果能正确使用，会发生很多千奇百怪的事！",en:"It\'s not really a seed, but a stone... But if you use it correctly, it\'ll sprout many terrible things!"};
descriptions["6254"]={cn:"雄猫毛比雌猫毛坚硬很多。对喵过敏的人不要触碰！",en:"These hairs are much less soft than those of the females. It\'s understandable why some are allergic to them!"};
descriptions["6256"]={cn:"让-图尔·格罗斯皮德曾经在著名香水奈香儿里放了一点点豆芙精华。",en:"These pheromones became fashionable when Jean-Trool Grospied used them for his famous perfume \'Le Mal.\'"};
descriptions["6257"]={cn:"信不信由你，其实虫脑比骑士的脑袋还大一点。",en:"Contrary to popular belief, this brain is larger than what you\'d find in a Iop\'s skull."};
descriptions["6293"]={cn:"又不是小孩子了，别抱着公仔睡了。",en:"Don\'t you think you\'re a little old to sleep with a stuffed animal?"};
descriptions["6363"]={cn:"肥沃的土壤，气味难闻。别不小心把它和你的午餐搞混了。",en:"This soil is fertile, but it doesn\'t smell very good at all. Don\'t get it mixed up with your lunch and dip bread into it, okay?"};
descriptions["6420"]={cn:"宝藏猎人用地穴兽獠牙来保护矿藏。如果你看到矿洞的墙壁上挂着这枚兽牙，这意味着：别碰我的矿！",en:"This tooth is used by Enutrofs to protect their mineral veins. If you see one hanging on the wall of a mine, the message is clear: no drilling!"};
descriptions["6421"]={cn:"坚硬有弹性，比一般的羊皮更优质！除非你和地穴兽一样眼瞎才分不清两者的优劣！",en:"Supple and strong, the leather is of much higher quality than ordinary Gobball leather! You\'d have to be as blind as a Drheller not to see the difference!"};
descriptions["6422"]={cn:"谁能想得到那个喜欢在自己的便便里打滚的动物能有这么丝滑的毛发？",en:"Who would have thought that the hair of an animal that likes to wallow in its own muck would be so silky?"};
descriptions["6485"]={cn:"平坦光滑，根据人体工程学原理设计。洗牌的时候总是能刚好分成数量对等的两半。",en:"Extra flat and ergonomic, these cards always split in half exactly at the right place."};
descriptions["6512"]={cn:"测试戒指等级 70 （一个就够了！）- 打地穴兽专用！",en:"Test ring lvl 70 (one\'s enough!) - To combat Drhellers only!"};
descriptions["6556"]={cn:"亲爱的，你是先洗澡，还是先吃晚餐？或者...",en:"These cards allow you to choose exactly which parts of your enemy you\'d like to have for dinner."};
descriptions["6570"]={cn:"在制造法杖前请先确认豆芙蛋已经被孵化了...",en:"It would have been wise to make sure the egg was empty before making this weapon..."};
descriptions["6571"]={cn:"完美搭配你的所有豆芙毛裤子。别装傻了！",en:"This wand will go perfectly with all the brightly-colored feathery underwear you own. Oh don\'t act all innocent!"};
descriptions["6572"]={cn:"没有人知道豆芙嘴是怎么被磨平的。我们只知道兽人大妈一定帮了不少忙。",en:"The process that made this Tofu beak flat remains a secret. All we can tell you is that we had a lot of help from Mama Bworks."};
descriptions["6576"]={cn:"一件十分强硬的胸甲。至少曾经是。",en:"This breastplate is very strong. Or at least, it was."};
descriptions["6578"]={cn:"为了让腰带穿戴舒适，制造者用了非常规的手法来软化腰带上的蓝宝石。虽然效果不明显，但是在社交场合依然熠熠生辉。",en:"To make this belt more comfortable, its creator used an ingenious method to soften the Sapphire. Not very useful, but it does shine in society."};
descriptions["6579"]={cn:"小心，穿着这双宝靴，会引得人们把你的腿从膝盖上撕下来！",en:"Take care, wearing these boots make people want to tear your legs off at the knees!"};
descriptions["6581"]={cn:"穿上这双靴子，会在行经之处留下燃烧的足迹。也能燃烧你的敌人。",en:"When you wear these boots, the earth will burn in your tracks. Your enemies too."};
descriptions["6582"]={cn:"显然，这条腰带的制作者与他羊群的交流方式很有趣。",en:"Clearly, the creator of this belt had a funny way of communicating with his flock."};
descriptions["6583"]={cn:"一件死人身上的破旧披风，肯定是幸运之兆。",en:"An old, worn cloak off a dead man. A lucky omen no doubt."};
descriptions["6584"]={cn:"西部英雄的必备配件，不幸的是，也是抢匪的配件。",en:"An essential accessory for somber heroes everywhere. Too bad for you, it\'s also the mark of sober heroes everywhere."};
descriptions["6585"]={cn:"不，这件背心跟征服了撕裂荒野的冒险者无关，它是因为在重复的洗涤中被撕裂而获得了这个名字。",en:"No, this vest didn\'t belong to an adventurer out to conquer the Vild Vest. It earned this nickname by getting torn in the wash. Repeatedly."};
descriptions["6586"]={cn:"你可能会好奇为什么会叫这名字，抬一下肩膀就会知道了。",en:"You\'re probably wondering why they have this name. Raise your shoulders and your question will be answered."};
descriptions["6588"]={cn:"对于任何自尊心强的宝藏猎人来说，这把铲子既能打晕敌人又能挖坟。二合一真好用！",en:"Indispensable to any self-respecting Enutrof, this shovel will serve both to stun the enemy and to dig his grave. Two in one!"};
descriptions["6598"]={cn:"怎能因为不够锐利就放弃刺痛敌人的机会？",en:"Just because you\'re not that sharp yourself, doesn\'t mean you can\'t poke holes in things."};
descriptions["6663"]={cn:"这根指针可以让敌人用作一根上吊用的绳子...",en:"This clock hand will give your opponents the rope to hang themselves with..."};
descriptions["6739"]={cn:"啊啊啊！你最终还是决定把戒指还给他！",en:"Aaaah! You\'ve finally decided to let him slip his ring over your finger!"};
descriptions["6780"]={cn:"松软的云朵很舒服，烦心事统统抛到脑后！",en:"If you\'re the type who always has your head in the clouds, you\'ll never be homesick!"};
descriptions["6781"]={cn:"好像披着一条毯子到处走动...毫无疑问这又是一种萨迪达风俗...",en:"Walking with a blanket on your back... Another Sadida custom, no doubt..."};
descriptions["6782"]={cn:"穿上它们，体验登上云端的感觉。",en:"Thanks to this pair of boots, you\'ll be on cloud nine. Or clouds 9a and 9b, to be precise!"};
descriptions["6783"]={cn:"给你带来了祥和的心境。",en:"This belt is so called because of the impulses of peace it provokes. Lots of peace. But where\'s the love?"};
descriptions["6785"]={cn:"能吸收任何冲击。你已经无惧任何肮脏的偷袭了。",en:"This breastplate will absorb all kinds of shocks. Now you\'re immune to head shots from dirty Gobbowl players."};
descriptions["6788"]={cn:"如果累了，可以靠在云朵护肩上睡一会儿。记得调整下高度，以防落枕。",en:"In case of fatigue, these epaulettes will allow you to take a nap. Consider alternating between the two to avoid getting a crick in your neck."};
descriptions["6791"]={cn:"木头做的头带，有问题吗？",en:"A headband made of wood, yeah, so what? What\'s the problem?"};
descriptions["6808"]={cn:"每次有姑娘要看货，你都得翻箱倒柜找出来？现在不用了，统统摆上货架！",en:"Instead of getting your gear out for every girl who asks to see it, display it in this case!"};
descriptions["6816"]={cn:"每个人都梦想拥有兔兔指环。",en:"Who hasn\'t dreamed of having a Wodent ring on their finger?"};
descriptions["6819"]={cn:"千万不要相信兔脚会带来好运...",en:"You\'d have to be really naive to believe a Wodent foot could bring good luck..."};
descriptions["6823"]={cn:"也就暖暖头用。",en:"A hat that will keep its wearer\'s assets warm."};
descriptions["6824"]={cn:"摆摊好！摆摊秒！我摆的摊位最热闹...",en:"How bazaar? Mda da da da da da, mmda da da, how Bazaar..."};
descriptions["6946"]={cn:"提神醒脑！解口渴更...大概这样了。但是据说，喝起来还不错。",en:"A fwesh stawt! It quenches thirst and... that\'s about it. But as they say, it\'s a good start."};
descriptions["6948"]={cn:"很多人不喜欢吃白灼胡萝卜。这一点也掩盖不了白灼是烹饪胡萝卜的最好方式。",en:"Many people don\'t like their Cawwots cooked. But they\'re tastiest this way!"};
descriptions["7026"]={cn:"哦！你终于决定向她求婚了！",en:"Aaaah! So you\'ve finally decided to put a ring on her finger!"};
descriptions["7030"]={cn:"你想永远把它留在身边？还是只想一夜激情？",en:"Is this the type of knife you\'ll want to keep by your side forever, or just for a day?"};
descriptions["7034"]={cn:"可以轻松砍下敌人的头。前提是你的敌人是个弱小的怪物。",en:"An axe for chopping off the head of your enemy, provided your enemy is a tiny, wimpy little monster."};
descriptions["7041"]={cn:"什么？看清楚，这是把魔杖，可不是什么火箭科技。",en:"Well, what? Look at it. It\'s a wand. It\'s not rocket science!"};
descriptions["7048"]={cn:"崇尚和平的人可以用这把锤子敲钉子。崇尚暴力的人则可以把钉子敲到敌人的头上。",en:"Those who don\'t like violence can use it to hammer nails. Those who love violence will use it to hammer nails into the skulls of their opponents."};
descriptions["7055"]={cn:"你不太会用剑？这太糟了...",en:"Too bad you\'re terrible with a sword..."};
descriptions["7056"]={cn:"可以让敌人用作一根上吊用的绳子...",en:"This clock hand will give your opponents the rope to hang themselves with..."};
descriptions["7119"]={cn:"阿宅必备。穿上它们，去任何地下城都好像在家里一样舒适。",en:"These slippers are perfect for stay-at-home adventurers. Slip them on and you\'ll feel right at home in any dungeon in the World of Twelve."};
descriptions["7120"]={cn:"有只兔兔缠在你的腰上？哇哦，放松点，现在流行这个！",en:"A Wodent \'round your pelvis? Woah, take it easy, hot stuff!"};
descriptions["7121"]={cn:"假设这也算是盔甲，可它实在保护不了什么。话说回来，穿着倒确实很性感！",en:"Granted, this armor won\'t really protect you from enemy attacks. You gotta admit, though, it does look pretty sexy!"};
descriptions["7314"]={cn:"很显然，过去很长一段时间里疯兔们一直把胡萝卜种子用作货币。真聪明！你看我们拿着卡玛却什么都种不出来。",en:"Apparently, a long time ago, the Wabbits used to use these seeds as money. Makes perfect sense! After all, you can\'t grow kamas!"};
descriptions["7343"]={cn:"这是道堪称极品的美味！当然，吃它之前你要去掉锡纸！",en:"This is a dish that will delight the most refined palates! Provided, of course, you remove the foil before eating!"};
descriptions["7352"]={cn:"生长于因卡纳姆的天界土壤之中，美丽典雅、气味宜人。与世无争的小花。因为漂亮，所以会被原谅。",en:"This beautiful, delicately-perfumed flower grows in the celestial soils of Incarnam. It doesn\'t really have much purpose, but it\'s pretty, so it can be forgiven."};
descriptions["7353"]={cn:"你手里握着的种子，它是如此脆弱，它不能忍受任何气候。 你只能在一个庇护袋或庇护领地里种植。",en:"You hold in your hands a seed which is so fragile that it can\'t stand any climate. You can only plant it in a Haven Bag or the Haven World."};
descriptions["7358"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few drops should suffice."};
