descriptions["7512"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["7570"]={cn:"难以置信！这条头带还可以当腰带用！少了它怎么过日子？",en:"Incredible! This band can also be worn as belt! How did you ever cope without it?"};
descriptions["7571"]={cn:"穿着木屐行走很难。在踩到了发酵的便便之后就更难了。",en:"Learning to walk in Getas is not easy. Strangely, it becomes much more difficult after a few liters of fermented muck."};
descriptions["7572"]={cn:"你的第一件道服，绝不是最后一件...",en:"Your first coat. And surely not the last..."};
descriptions["7573"]={cn:"早就告诉你们了，这当然不会是最后一件...",en:"We told you it wouldn\'t be the last..."};
descriptions["7574"]={cn:"很显然马加罗夫再也不用哼哼了。这毫无意义。就像你一样。",en:"This must be the hat Magalouf was talking about in his rhyme \'eenie meenie hatty ho.\' This information is completely useless. Much like yourself."};
descriptions["7575"]={cn:"这些卡片可以精准地将伊欧普人的脑袋砍成完整的两半，这只是其中一个作用！",en:"These cards are so precise they could cut a Iop\'s brain clean in half. And that\'s saying something!"};
descriptions["7576"]={cn:"当熊猫武僧喝多了之后会动不动就脱下腰带。好吧，实际上他们经常光着屁股。",en:"This is the famous belt that Pandawans tend to take off when they\'ve drunk too much. Let\'s just say they don\'t wear it too often."};
descriptions["7577"]={cn:"在熊猫武僧晚宴上，有个古老习俗，大家都会把自己的腰带绑在酒吧的门闩上，这样不会醉倒。或者他们没办法把你扔出去...",en:"On those well-watered Pandawan evenings, there\'s an old tradition of attaching your belt to the bar of the tavern so as not to fall over. Or so they can\'t throw you out..."};
