descriptions["7932"]={cn:"饱满又漂亮的麦粒。",en:"A brilliant and beautiful grain."};
descriptions["7977"]={cn:"黑色布丁，气味刺鼻，由乌鸦血制成。还好有苹朵可以缓和口味。",en:"If the pudding is black and tastes as strong as it smells, it has been made from Crobak\'s Blood. Luckily, the Api is there to hide the taste."};
