descriptions["8046"]={cn:"从一只活的啾啾身上拔下羽毛之后，羽毛会变成紫色。感受掉毛啾啾的愤怒吧。",en:"When Piwi feathers are pulled out of a living specimen, they turn purple. This symbolizes the anger of the defeathered Piwi."};
descriptions["8047"]={cn:"冒着热气的小面包，销路很广！",en:"This Farle bread is selling like...  Uh hot Farle bread!"};
descriptions["8048"]={cn:"啾啾馅的面包？面包馅的啾啾？随你怎么想。",en:"Piwi-stuffed bread. Bread-stuffed Piwi? Depends who you\'re talking to."};
descriptions["8050"]={cn:"150 卡玛，因爱铸就。",en:"150 little Kamas, minted with love."};
descriptions["8051"]={cn:"掉落在地上的碎石者的一部分碎片。上面刻着古朴的石器时代艺术，看起来十分有男人味。",en:"This cutlass is actually a piece of Crackler that was found on the floor and decorated with rock art to make it appear more manly."};
descriptions["8052"]={cn:"这个工具聪明的设计是为了...收割，没错，两把刀片增加了精准性和亲密性！",en:"A tool cleverly designed to...  Cut. Yes, but with two blades, for greater accuracy and closeness!"};
descriptions["8053"]={cn:"如果你家里有点田，学好这本书，给自己种出一个未来。",en:"With this book, you\'ll be able to learn all you knead to know about how to make some dough without getting burned."};
descriptions["8054"]={cn:"如果不马上吃掉，绵球会来帮你吃！",en:"If you don\'t eat it straight away, a Gobball will do that for you!"};
descriptions["8055"]={cn:"尽管面包卷很漂亮，你最后还是会讨厌这种面包。不要被外表欺骗了！",en:"Despite its generous curves, you\'ll end up tiring of this Blonde Loaf. Don\'t be taken in by appearances!"};
descriptions["8056"]={cn:"香脆可口，唤醒你的所有味觉！有人甚至会为了它拼上性命！",en:"This Painstry is so good, it can awaken all your senses! Some people would even kill for a bite."};
descriptions["8057"]={cn:"不要和生姜头搞混了。",en:"Not to be confused with Gingerhead Men."};
descriptions["8058"]={cn:"忘却它的名字吧，你只需要记住意式面包的香脆口感。",en:"Forget the name and let yourself be overcome by the taste of hazelnut."};
descriptions["8059"]={cn:"很硬的面包。在室外风干后可以用来当保龄球瓶。",en:"Round Bread is so compact that it\'s often used to play bowling if it sits out too long!"};
descriptions["8063"]={cn:"只有伐木工才能阻止这根树枝生长。",en:"Only a lumberjack can stop this cutting."};
descriptions["8064"]={cn:"梦想种出饱满果实的人有福了。",en:"This will delight anyone who\'s always dreamed of growing beautiful nuts."};
descriptions["8065"]={cn:"你手里有五十个苹朵，足够做十个苹朵派和一百个黑苹朵布丁。",en:"Theoretically, you hold in your hand fifty Apis, which is enough to make ten Pies and the equivalent of a hundred Apple black puddings."};
descriptions["8066"]={cn:"干燥易燃，在森林中请谨慎使用。",en:"A little help for burnt out forests."};
descriptions["8067"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["8068"]={cn:"人们总是说白杨树在潮湿的洞里生长最快。",en:"They always say that a Pooplar is most at home in a moist hole."};
descriptions["8069"]={cn:"这可能是最可爱的树枝了。伐木工人不会无缘无故地称这棵树为“魅力”！",en:"This is quite possibly the loveliest cutting around. Lumberjacks don\'t call the tree it grows into \"the Charm\" for nothing!"};
descriptions["8071"]={cn:"采矿要从娃娃抓起。推荐18岁以下人群阅读。",en:"Mining must be learned early, so this book is not recommended for anyone aged 18 or over."};
descriptions["8072"]={cn:"初级牧人指导手册。配有彩色插图以及各类毛发样本。",en:"An illustrated guide for junior trappers. With lots of pretty pictures and hair samples inside."};
descriptions["8073"]={cn:"这本书很厚重，难以消化，完全可以用来碾面粉。",en:"This book is very heavy, and totally indigestible, but it is perfect for grinding flour."};
descriptions["8077"]={cn:"上钩了？没上钩？哦哦！我钓到了一条龟鱼！",en:"Do they bite? Not a bite? Ohh! I got a Chefish!"};
descriptions["8079"]={cn:"这株植物会自己爬起来...",en:"Now here\'s a plant that pushes up its own daisies."};
descriptions["8080"]={cn:"点击两下来把整组古代资源转换成新的资源。古代资源需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["8081"]={cn:"即便是邦塔的武器库，也没有像咕哩一样武装到牙齿。",en:"Even Bonta\'s weapons store isn\'t as well equipped and dangerous as this tooth."};
descriptions["8082"]={cn:"割掉海星的触手是野蛮的行径！不过它很快就能长回来的，别太内疚了。",en:"Cutting off a star fish\'s tentacle is a barbaric act. It will grow back though, so don\'t feel too guilty."};
descriptions["8084"]={cn:"就算强如树精，依然要经受青春期的磨练...",en:"Even Treechnids must endure the inconvenience of puberty..."};
descriptions["8085"]={cn:"点击两下来把整组古代资源转换成新的资源。古代资源需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["8086"]={cn:"邦塔的年轻古惑仔们最喜欢用狼爪来恶作剧。",en:"Boowolf Paws are used by Bonta\'s young rebels to carry out their deadly hoaxes."};
descriptions["8087"]={cn:"没有什么比万事可乐更提神的了！",en:"Nothing like a nice cool root beer on a sunny afternoon to forget your latest heartbreak!"};
descriptions["8089"]={cn:"致米米：即便不能温暖你自由的心，至少也能点亮路灯。",en:"Even if the flame doesn\'t warm your lonely heart, it will let you see in the dark."};
descriptions["8090"]={cn:"收录于著名的《旅行者传送指南》丛书中。",en:"This is from the famous \"Zaapackers guide...\" collection."};
descriptions["8091"]={cn:"除了难闻的啤酒味以外，肩甲还是很结实的。",en:"Musty root beer smell aside, these epaulettes take some beating."};
descriptions["8092"]={cn:"木质的胸甲：不含塑化剂，你懂的。",en:"A wooden breastplate: good when you\'re feeling a bit plastic, you know!"};
descriptions["8093"]={cn:"破碎的心，重振起来！",en:"This amulet is the rallying symbol for broken hearted souls."};
descriptions["8095"]={cn:"煮焦了，没错，不过毕竟心意在。",en:"Burnt, yes, but served with love."};
descriptions["8096"]={cn:"一块小面包。润滑可口，易于消化。",en:"A slight, light brioche! So delicious that it will have appeared on your hips before it\'s even finished melting in your mouth. Yummmmm!"};
descriptions["8097"]={cn:"这枝树枝的品质在其余之上。",en:"One small step for a small Elm."};
descriptions["8104"]={cn:"超大的鲟鱼...如果你不喜欢吃鱼，大可以把它们用作武器！",en:"This sturgeon is massive... if you don\'t like fish you can always use it as a weapon!"};
descriptions["8105"]={cn:"献给口味特殊的你。",en:"When he was a cook, Captain Igloute loved to prepare Breaded Fish!"};
descriptions["8106"]={cn:"谁说喵喵怕水的？",en:"Who said Bow Meows didn\'t like water?"};
descriptions["8107"]={cn:"据说脾气很坏。也许这就是它们很难吃的缘故。",en:"It is well known that anchovies have terrible tempers. That\'s probably why they taste so bitter."};
descriptions["8108"]={cn:"柔软蓬松，谁不想摸一下毛鳐？",en:"Who has never dreamed of touching something as soft as Hairy Ray?"};
descriptions["8109"]={cn:"它看起来很累了...很明显在打哈欠。",en:"This Grawn looks wealy tired... It\'s pwetty *yawn* obvious."};
descriptions["8110"]={cn:"据说三文鱼是濒临灭绝的物种，当你吞下它的时候不要考虑这个...",en:"It is said that Salamon is an endangered species. Try not to think about that as you swallow..."};
descriptions["8111"]={cn:"肉质鲜美。",en:"This fish\'s name derives from the old fishing tradition of lowering your trousers and mooning fishermen in other boats when you got a good catch."};
descriptions["8112"]={cn:"别多想了！龙鲤和龙鸟一点关系都没有。龙鲤比龙鸟聪明多了，它住在水里，更重要的是，你不能骑它...",en:"Forget it! This Dragocarp is in no way related to Dragoturkeys. It is much more intelligent, it lives in water and, unfortunately, no, you can\'t ride it..."};
descriptions["8113"]={cn:"鱼的尺寸各有不同，你的特别大。",en:"Loots come in all sizes. Yours is huge."};
descriptions["8114"]={cn:"不要小看它，它会发飙的...",en:"When called common, this shark turns red with anger..."};
descriptions["8115"]={cn:"红烧白灼两相宜，切片生食亦爽口。大家都爱吃！",en:"Hot or cold, sliced or whole, with sauce or chips, Perch is the new fad and everyone wants a piece!"};
descriptions["8116"]={cn:"手里有条剑鱼最方便的就是你不用再带刀了。",en:"The best thing about Swordfish Tench is that it comes with its own knife!"};
descriptions["8117"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["8118"]={cn:"不仅仅是鼻孔，而是整个鼻腔。注意细节。",en:"This is not a nose, it\'s a snout. Note the subtle difference."};
descriptions["8120"]={cn:"指挥官库斯托从没告诉你这是哪一种海洋生物的肉...",en:"Commander Koosto himself has never been able to say which creature kindly grew this flesh..."};
descriptions["8121"]={cn:"点击两下来把整组古代资源转换成新的资源。古代资源需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["8122"]={cn:"丢掉礼节，大快朵颐！",en:"Manners cost nothing..."};
descriptions["8124"]={cn:"地穴兽用手捂住它的心。等等...那不是你的心吗？",en:"This Drheller has his hand on his heart. Or...  is that your heart?"};
descriptions["8127"]={cn:"这张废纸是什么？丢掉丢掉，对你一点用都没有！",en:"What is this old scrap of paper? Chuck it away, you don\'t need that anymore!"};
descriptions["8128"]={cn:"超级实用！你能把你早上喝剩的羊奶，忘记穿的拖鞋，刚睡醒的喵喵，甚至另一个货架...都放在上面。不瞒您说，真的能放好多东西。",en:"This is very practical! You can display your Gobbette Milk, your slippers, another display window, your Bow Meow... Pretty much anything you don\'t know where else to put, basically."};
descriptions["8135"]={cn:"修剪树枝的艺术。考虑到宝藏猎人眼力不行，特意用大号字体印刷。",en:"The art of branching out. Written in large print for Enutrofs."};
descriptions["8136"]={cn:"提高你采花的技巧。别害羞，脸皮要厚！",en:"Yes, it\'s a manual for improving your flower-picking skills. There is no shame in that!"};
descriptions["8137"]={cn:"指挥官库斯托亲自撰写，散发着一股蚌蚌腥味。书页之中，也许还夹着几颗沙子。",en:"Written by Commander Koosto himself, this book smells of mussels. You will probably find a few grains of sand stuck between the pages."};
descriptions["8138"]={cn:"从狼肋排到色拉海洋，本书包含了200多个食谱，足够让你吃到腻。",en:"From Boowolf sirloin to the sea salad, this book contains over 200 recipes to annihilate your appetite."};
descriptions["8142"]={cn:"野外求生必备手册之一，它教你如何在击败野兽之后把它们回收利用。你身边的资源有限，别浪费一丁一点。",en:"This book is part of the adventurer\'s survival kit. It tells you what to do with your enemies\' hides once you\'ve skinned them."};
descriptions["8143"]={cn:"想要在战斗中获胜，绝对少不了一身制作精良的装备。这本书能指导你身为英雄该如何准备行头。",en:"You need to have good, solid equipment if you want to actually win some fights: this book will ensure you have the makings of a hero."};
descriptions["8144"]={cn:"发现书页都黏在一起了吗？因为这书是用树灵脂写的。",en:"Don\'t be surprised if the pages of this book stick together, it was written using Treechnid sap."};
descriptions["8145"]={cn:"你会发现这本书才是真正的传家宝...",en:"You\'ll see this book is a real treasure..."};
descriptions["8146"]={cn:"如果你不识字，你直接把它穿上试试...",en:"If you don\'t know how to read, you could always test it out as an armor..."};
descriptions["8152"]={cn:"放心，鼠小弟不会要这团杂毛的。",en:"The Rat-Tattoo is a sneaky rodent thief who won\'t think twice about stealing your kamas. No need to lose sleep about stealing his fur then!"};
descriptions["8153"]={cn:"“哎！喂！嘿！我们被困在这里了！”别叫了，就算叫破喉咙也没有人会来救你的。",en:"Heigh-ho, heigh-ho, we\'re stuck here in this hole.\' Unfortunately, no amount of singing this song will get you out of prison any faster."};
descriptions["8159"]={cn:"长夜漫漫无心睡眠，为你的室友磨指甲的理想选择。",en:"Ideal for nights spent perfecting your cell mates\' manicures."};
descriptions["8162"]={cn:"因为埋在海底的时间太长，始终散发着海洋的气味。知足吧，起码没有靴子前主人的脚臭味...",en:"This shoe smells of the sea because it\'s spent so long underwater. At least you can thank your lucky stars it doesn\'t smell of its last owner\'s feet..."};
descriptions["8163"]={cn:"世界上首款采用全方位通风系统的短裤，让你享受风吹过的感觉。",en:"The first underpants with integrated ventilation. Ideal for those who love weeing in the wind."};
descriptions["8171"]={cn:"即便在你把它栽下去的时候，依然在哭泣。",en:"It still wails even when you plant it!"};
descriptions["8172"]={cn:"现在，有个可以哭泣的理由了！",en:"Now it has a good reason to cry!"};
descriptions["8176"]={cn:"一点带有唾液以及滋滋胃酸的血液...呃，真是可口！",en:"A bit of blood mixed with saliva and a touch of Moskito gastric acid...  umm, tasty!"};
descriptions["8177"]={cn:"传说如果年轻的未婚植物术士把蟾涎抹在脸上，她们就会变成公主。快来试试！",en:"According to legend, if young unmarried female Sadidas dab this on their face, they turn into princesses. Go figure!"};
descriptions["8178"]={cn:"滋滋没翅膀走不了多远，拍死它易如反掌。",en:"Moskitos can\'t get very far without their wings, which is even more reason for you to pluck them off."};
descriptions["8179"]={cn:"舔邮票很管用，还可以用来获得年轻姑娘们的芳心。",en:"Very practical for stamp licking, this Toad Tongue can also be used to trick young girls in search of Prince Charming."};
descriptions["8180"]={cn:"点击两下来把整组古代资源转换成新的资源。古代资源需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["8181"]={cn:"点击两下来把整组古代资源转换成新的资源。古代资源需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["8182"]={cn:"无论油炸或清蒸，都难以去除怪味。",en:"Fried or steamed, these legs always have the same foul taste."};
descriptions["8187"]={cn:"到底有什么用途？",en:"What can it be used for?"};
descriptions["8189"]={cn:"简单来说，如何打招呼。",en:"Or, quite simply, how to say hello."};
descriptions["8190"]={cn:"良好的坐姿能保护你的臀部。\n（加速生命自然恢复速度。）",en:"Everyone knows that sitting properly preserves your patootie.\n(Speeds up natural HP regeneration.)"};
descriptions["8191"]={cn:"或者，想想怎样才能带头鼓掌并且看起来不像个蠢货。",en:"Or, how to start a round of applause without looking like a total idiot."};
descriptions["8192"]={cn:"教你像明星一样打哈欠！",en:"Yawn and look classy? Yep, it can be done!"};
descriptions["8193"]={cn:"你也许找不到宝藏，但是你肯定能了解宝藏猎人勇敢的心。",en:"You might not find more treasure, but you\'ll certainly have the style and class of the gold seekers of yesteryear about you, that\'s for sure."};
descriptions["8194"]={cn:"教会你迅速变得怒不可遏，其实仅仅是因为喘不过气来。",en:"This scroll will teach you a simple method to make yourself extremely angry very quickly, and it\'s all based on a simple lack of breathing."};
descriptions["8195"]={cn:"你在表演课上没学过“害怕”这个表情吗？",en:"Did they teach \"Horror\" at your acting class?"};
descriptions["8196"]={cn:"不能教会你如何阅读，但是能让你看起来像学者。",en:"The scroll won\'t teach you how to read, but flicking through it will make it look as though you can."};
descriptions["8197"]={cn:"萨迪达姑娘们必读。",en:"A little guide that numerous Sadidettes could do with reading."};
descriptions["8199"]={cn:"流泪很简单，特别是当你浑身长毛的时候。只要拔根毛就行了！",en:"The technique is a simple one, especially if you\'re hairy! Just pull a clump out in one go!"};
descriptions["8200"]={cn:"虽然不太礼貌，但是对于骑士来说，有时候指指点点地嘲笑才是最好的回答。",en:"Although it\'s not usually seen as being very polite, sometimes pointing and laughing is the most appropriate response to Iops."};
descriptions["8201"]={cn:"面对不善于讲笑话的宝藏猎人的高效武器。",en:"Very handy for not upsetting an Enutrof that tells terrible jokes."};
descriptions["8202"]={cn:"根据米歇尔的研究，这种石头其实可以食用。虽然难以消化，但是能让你练成不动如山的绝技。",en:"Based on a Madalton recipe, this pebble has gastronomic virtues. A bit heavy to digest, but it sits like a stone."};
descriptions["8204"]={cn:"有一种失传的古老传统，要使用这种又软又圆的面包互相战斗。这是自从切片面包之后最好的东西了！",en:"An ancient custom which consists of fighting in the middle of the ring using this soft, round bap. It\'s the best thing since sliced bread!"};
descriptions["8205"]={cn:"还记得新鲜出炉的面包发出的香喷喷的气味吗...",en:"Remember dreaming of those freshly baked cakes from the local bakery..."};
descriptions["8207"]={cn:"一次露营中，我差点被一个蝴蝶饼噎死！ - 杰克·鲁博",en:"This one time, at band camp, I nearly choked on a Bretzel! \n- Jack Lumber"};
descriptions["8208"]={cn:"由金黄面粉制成，香气四溢。",en:"Made from gold, frankincense and... urgh..."};
descriptions["8209"]={cn:"与你的期待相反，这种面包并不是枪手做的。",en:"Contrary to what one might expect, Schwoops isn\'t used to make this bread."};
descriptions["8210"]={cn:"别在意名字，这种小吃在学校里很流行的！",en:"Don\'t be fooled by its name, this treat is really popular at school!"};
descriptions["8211"]={cn:"很多女生希望变得和萨迪达少女一样苗条，她们需要的是全麦面包。",en:"Whole bread is for those who wish they were as skinny as young Sadida girls."};
descriptions["8212"]={cn:"不太容易消化的面包。很强大的武器。",en:"This bread isn\'t very easy to digest. Which makes it a fearful weapon."};
descriptions["8213"]={cn:"舒克舒克舒克，开飞机的舒克...",en:"\"Captain Cockle, you\'re not from our bakery, but from the depths of the night! Captain Cockle!\""};
descriptions["8214"]={cn:"派克汉姆曾经对他妻子说：亲爱的，你做的恭敬派真是临门的一脚好球。他并不知道这种甜点其实是象征了妻子无法容忍丈夫的不忠。",en:"Davit Peckham once said to his wife: \"Honey, your Humble Pie is a real kick in the balls.\" Little did he know that this dish is often prepared by those who can\'t tolerate their husband\'s infidelities."};
descriptions["8215"]={cn:"它的存在证明了一件事！这是与流行的看法截然相反的，魔族们可以把它做的如此甜。",en:"It\'s proven! Contrary to popular belief, Shushus can be really sweet."};
descriptions["8216"]={cn:"这么跟人打招呼能让你显得很厉害。",en:"This scroll will teach you to say hello like a real Karate master, without the inconvenience of having to grow a long, white beard!"};
descriptions["8217"]={cn:"记载着管理十二世界生态系统的基本法则。",en:"A book dealing with the precise rules that govern the ecosystem of the World of Twelve."};
descriptions["8224"]={cn:"挑剔的骸骨军，行军时总会弄丢一堆腿骨。",en:"If you happen to run into this Chafer, he might have a bone or two to pick with you!"};
descriptions["8225"]={cn:"点击两下来把整组古代资源转换成新的资源。古代资源需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["8226"]={cn:"上面并没有很多烂泥，但是看起来还是很恶心。",en:"There\'s not Mushd to it and it looks a bit Mushd but there we have it; a Mushd Hand."};
descriptions["8228"]={cn:"嗯嗯...老实说，煮熟之后，我还真说不准它是不是鲟鱼...",en:"Hmmm... To tell the truth, now that it\'s boiled, it\'s hard to be sure it\'s a fish..."};
descriptions["8229"]={cn:"鸡肉味，嘎嘣脆！",en:"This recipe existed long before Captain Eyebirds was born."};
descriptions["8230"]={cn:"好鼻子接近禁止！这种寿司的确很棒...就是真难闻！",en:"Sensitive noses should keep away! This sushi is good... but it really stinks!"};
descriptions["8231"]={cn:"虽然气味难闻，但是久经烹煮，肉质鲜嫩多汁。你敢吃吗？",en:"This Ray may not give off the most appetizing odor, but when it\'s well-prepared, its flesh opens up and becomes quite succulent. Do you dare to taste it?"};
descriptions["8232"]={cn:"如果不想留下满嘴鱼腥味，吃完后就嚼一块达意口香糖。",en:"If you don\'t want to have fish breath, chew a Mint Jelly after your meal."};
descriptions["8233"]={cn:"灭菌兽人乳酪的加入后产生的味道让人欲罢不能，萨隆。",en:"Not to be confused with the Bwork antiseptic cream, Salvon."};
descriptions["8244"]={cn:"哟吼吼，草莓味的。常年不洗，绅士最爱！",en:"These Ecaflipette panties have been carefully washed in \"Purrsil\" washing powder."};
descriptions["8247"]={cn:"质量无懈可击。怪不得某骑士可以自由翱翔！",en:"These boots are in impeccable condition. It\'s not surprising for someone who did most of his traveling by air!"};
descriptions["8248"]={cn:"追踪飞鸟的最好办法是给它套个环！",en:"The best way to keep track of a bird is to ring it!"};
descriptions["8249"]={cn:"一根针，几根线以及从一只腐烂的乌鸦身上获得的羽毛若干...现在你拥有了十二世界中最时髦的披风！",en:"A needle, some thread and a few feathers taken from a decomposing Crobak... and now you have one of the most fashionable capes in the World of Twelve!"};
descriptions["8257"]={cn:"每走一步都伴着一声乌鸦惨叫。光靠声音就可以把敌人吓走了，不战而屈人之兵。",en:"These Croboots emit a Crow squawk with every step you take. You can make the enemy flee just by warning them of your imminent arrival."};
descriptions["8258"]={cn:"一件可以拿来在地下酒馆里炫耀的胸甲。",en:"A feathery thing that you can take great pleasure in showing off in the most squalid tavern in town."};
descriptions["8259"]={cn:"有效防止腰痛。也许还有别的效果？穿上之后才知道。",en:"This belt is supposed to improve back trouble. Or is that the other way round? You won\'t know until you try it on!"};
descriptions["8264"]={cn:"木头的鱼竿比竹子鱼竿更好用，可以甩得更远...你可以钓更多的鱼！",en:"A wooden rod is better than a bamboo one because it fishes further... You can do even better, though!"};
descriptions["8265"]={cn:"走过路过不要错过！高级石片！",en:"Tiger! Upper Cutlass!"};
descriptions["8266"]={cn:"我爱镰刀，镰刀爱我。这把镰刀能让你收获更多的谷物。",en:"Nice to scythe you, to scythe you nice! This scythe will allow you to collect A FEW more grains per harvest."};
descriptions["8267"]={cn:"上一把还没砍几下就崩了，这一把至少能砍几下再崩...",en:"Your last one was better at crushing than cutting, and this one\'s better at smashing than crushing..."};
descriptions["8268"]={cn:"挖，拼命挖。体力劳动的汗水是最甘甜的。",en:"Mine, pick, then, as you carry the fruits of your labor home, sing: \"Hi-ho, hi-ho, it\'s home from work we go!\""};
descriptions["8269"]={cn:"据说盖特菲克用这把钩刀来收割他的鼻毛，但是没人知道更他是如何做到的...",en:"It is claimed that Getafiks used this billhook to harvest his own nasal hair. No one knows what he did with it..."};
descriptions["8288"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["8359"]={cn:"饱含着爱心烘焙而成，吃下后心情愉悦。",en:"Kneaded and baked with love, these superb baps will get more than one person excited."};
descriptions["8370"]={cn:"现在你可以弹弹约翰·列蒙的歌了。注意不要把他从坟墓里气活过来...",en:"You\'re going to be able to play all of Jon Lemon\'s songs. Try not to make him turn over in his grave though..."};
descriptions["8371"]={cn:"告诉世界老子有的是钱，一块钱也是钱。",en:"Show the World that you\'re rolling in money... or at least make them think that."};
descriptions["8372"]={cn:"挠痒不求人！",en:"Itch that scratch of yours!"};
descriptions["8373"]={cn:"好新鲜的空气！",en:"Like a breath of fresh air!"};
descriptions["8375"]={cn:"从现在开始，你多了个漂亮的背包。随便你往里面塞什么。",en:"From now on, this udder will make a very nice pocket. It\'s up to you to decide what you want to keep in it."};
descriptions["8377"]={cn:"至少在你尝试使用你的新技能的时候它不会进行反击，更重要的是，它不需要食物而且也不需要更换底座。",en:"At least this one won\'t answer back when you try out your new spells. What\'s more, he doesn\'t eat and you don\'t have to change his litter tray."};
descriptions["8379"]={cn:"巨魔杀手们视巨魔腰带为荣耀。",en:"Trool slayers normally wear their belts as a trophy. Well, the biggest ones do."};
descriptions["8380"]={cn:"让巨魔颤抖的武器。",en:"This is just about the only weapon a Trool\'s scared of!"};
descriptions["8381"]={cn:"戴着这件头盔，你会拥有很多乐趣！比如勾引一个女巨魔...",en:"With this scalp on your head, you\'re going to have so much fun! You might even manage to seduce a female Trool..."};
descriptions["8382"]={cn:"但愿这双靴子和闻起来一样让人无法接近...",en:"Let\'s hope these boots are as solid as they are smelly..."};
descriptions["8383"]={cn:"谁能缝一件漂亮的奴隶制服出来？谁能？",en:"Who\'s going to be able to make a magnificent slave suit? What? Who?"};
descriptions["8384"]={cn:"点击两下来把整组古代资源转换成新的资源。古代资源需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["8385"]={cn:"自从这件胸甲上市之后，人们发现了一种崭新的战斗方式...长毛攻击。",en:"Since this breastplate arrived on the market, a new fighting technique has been seen on the battlefield. It\'s known as \'tufting.\'"};
descriptions["8396"]={cn:"一天一个苹朵，医生不来找我！",en:"An Api a day keeps the Doctor away!"};
descriptions["8398"]={cn:"一旦在市场里被发现，会引起疯抢，所以抓紧点...或者也可以时不时看看背包还在不在自己手上。",en:"They go nuts for this sack down at the market so hold on tight... and maybe give it a reassuring scratch every now and again."};
descriptions["8399"]={cn:"其实只是一块木头。",en:"Not to be confused with the famous storyteller."};
descriptions["8400"]={cn:"讨厌漂亮，只爱丑女？这件丑上加丑的披风就是你进入丑女广场的贵宾卡！",en:"Fed up of looking stylish? This unwelcome addition to your favorite outfit will get you VIP access to the Ugly Square!"};
descriptions["8401"]={cn:"想变丑？这顶假发能让你进入丑女广场的VIP通道！",en:"Fed up of looking stylish? This unwelcome addition to your favorite outfit will get you VIP access to the Ugly Square!"};
descriptions["8402"]={cn:"讨厌漂亮，只爱丑女？这件丑上加丑的披风就是你进入丑女广场的贵宾卡！",en:"Fed up of looking stylish? This unwelcome addition to your favorite outfit will get you VIP access to the Ugly Square!"};
descriptions["8403"]={cn:"丝滑柔顺，让你仿佛置身云层中！可以从国家区域地下城中的宝箱怪获得。",en:"Silky and soft, this cotton with take you to cloud 9! You can find some in the mimic chests in Nation dungeons."};
descriptions["8404"]={cn:"不是说这种布匹会出声，没那么高级，只是说它这种俗气的色彩名声很响亮。",en:"This cloth isn\'t \'loud\' for its overdeveloped vocal organ, but for its somewhat garish color."};
descriptions["8405"]={cn:"中号的帽子，带有疯克与迪斯科的风格。也能当作摔跤比赛的头盔使用。",en:"A size M which exudes the sweet smell of funk and disco. It can also be used as a helmet during catch tournaments."};
descriptions["8406"]={cn:"在这件衣服之下，你将会看到一张鲜血淋淋的头皮，它是属于一个人的，毋庸置疑！",en:"Under the cloth, you\'ll find a nice, bloody piece of scalp. This used to belong to a head, no doubt about it!"};
descriptions["8407"]={cn:"有一种古老的消遣游戏在土匪之间流传，就是闲着无聊做做针线活。",en:"The old Riktus pastime of \"spinning a yarn\" comes from the fact that they used to spend their free time making their clothes."};
descriptions["8408"]={cn:"点击两下来把整组古代资源转换成新的资源。古代资源需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["8409"]={cn:"很漂亮的缠腰布。也许短了一点，但是真的很漂亮。",en:"Drape yourself in this standard and you will have a very pretty loincloth. It might be a bit short, of course, but pretty all the same!"};
descriptions["8410"]={cn:"点击两下来把整组古代资源转换成新的资源。古代资源需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["8412"]={cn:"这就是通常说的眼冒金星！",en:"Now that\'s what you call having stars in your eyes!"};
descriptions["8414"]={cn:"倒数三秒。三，二，一，走你！",en:"I have three seconds to tell you that this Canoon Powder is the boooooomb!"};
descriptions["8418"]={cn:"不停地挠主人的手心，让无聊的冒险者在战斗中享受额外乐趣。",en:"This clock hand has the annoying tendency of tickling its bearer\'s hand, which adds an extra element of challenge in battle for the more blasé adventurer."};
