descriptions["8523"]={cn:"这把古怪的弓是为一个小村庄里固步自封的国王专门打造的。他十分喜欢同时发出两只箭矢来炫耀威力。",en:"This unconventional bow was designed specifically for the self-proclaimed king of a village of peasants, who loved showing off by firing two arrows simultaneously."};
