descriptions["8568"]={cn:"如果剧烈晃动这个木棒，它会开始散发火花，最后会爆炸，不幸的库奇有一次去使用这木棒，结果到燃烧结束时依然卡在腰带上面...",en:"If you vigorously shake this staff, it will start giving off sparks and eventually explode. The unfortunate Kutcher Endoff once went running with it still attached to his belt..."};
