descriptions["8571"]={cn:"镶铁的手杖，雕刻着绵球图案。用来击打别人的时候，你会听到一声响亮的“哎呦”！",en:"This steel rimmed staff with its Gobball carving really commands respect. When you use it to hit someone, the only noise to break the revered silence will be \"Ow\"!"};
