descriptions["8622"]={cn:"毫无疑问，这柄法杖能毁坏一切！无论是骷髅、软骨，还是其他任何东西都不堪一击！聆听敌人骨头粉碎的美妙音乐吧...",en:"There are no two ways about it, this staff crushes everything! Skull, cartilage, everything! That will be music to the ears of those you who like the sound of bones cracking..."};
