descriptions["8908"]={cn:"阿玛克纳人的基本思想被铭刻在这把斧子里。Claus Ansipedi 认为，给那些愚蠢的狗带点文化气息是个好主意。真是浪费时间！最后他的头骨被打了个稀巴烂。",en:"Basic Amaknian ideas are engraved into this ax. Claus Ansipedi, thought it would be a good idea to bring a semblance of culture to those cretinous dogs. What a waste of time! He ended up with his skull bashed in."};
