descriptions["9242"]={cn:"一般都是把皇冠戴在头上。你却又一次选择了一种与众不同的时尚...",en:"Normally, you wear the crown on your head. But it looks like you\'ve decided to make a bold fashion statement, once again..."};
descriptions["9243"]={cn:"曾经是十二世界中深受人们喜爱的游戏。现在，它们成为了致命的武器。",en:"In the past, these cards were part of a much loved game in the World of Twelve. Nowadays, they\'re fearful weapons."};
descriptions["9244"]={cn:"由尸体上的残骸制成。现在你知道为什么这套卡牌很容易弯曲了吧。",en:"These cards are made from the remains of corpses, which makes them particularly supple."};
