descriptions["9247"]={cn:"横扫饥饿，做回自己...能使已死之人精力充沛的饮料。",en:"Full of beans - that\'s the slogan for this drink that can awaken the dead."};
descriptions["9249"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["9251"]={cn:"喝的时候捂住鼻子：并不仅仅是因为阿玛克纳传统的缘故，而是喝下去后有一股淡淡的羊尿味...",en:"Hold your nose when drinking this: not only is it an Amaknian tradition, it also masks the aftertaste of Bow Meow pee..."};
descriptions["9252"]={cn:"臭烘烘的一把剑，不要轻易拿出来！让一只皇家绵球闻到它自己的臭气可不是个好主意...",en:"This sword absolutely stinks, but try not to let it show! It\'s not a great idea to tell a Royal Gobball he smells..."};
descriptions["9253"]={cn:"也许你不相信，但是它的伤害和它的气味一样强！",en:"You\'d never have believed it, but it hurts as bad as it smells! What power!"};
descriptions["9254"]={cn:"与其像王子一样草率进攻，为什么不像个国王一样稳重抵抗？",en:"Instead of fighting like a prince, why not defend yourself like a king?"};
descriptions["9256"]={cn:"拥有如此柔顺的绒毛，你现在理解为什么那些绵团喜欢围着皇家绵球转了！",en:"With such a fine fleece, you can understand why all the Gobblettes are so keen to get their hands on the Royal Gobball!"};
descriptions["9257"]={cn:"高档，但是气味难闻。这个护符会让你的皇室朋友十分嫉妒。",en:"Smelly, but royal, this amulet will make your regal friends very jealous."};
descriptions["9268"]={cn:"要是你想引人发笑，建议你嘴里叼根香蕉，不停的说“萝卜萝卜萝卜”。",en:"If you really want to make people laugh, you should try saying \"Tuberbulb\" over and over again with a Citranana in your mouth."};
descriptions["9269"]={cn:"有可能是个滋滋卵。种植在你的庇护袋之前，请三思。",en:"This could just as easily be a Moskito egg, so think twice before planting it in your home."};
descriptions["9270"]={cn:"坚强的兰花，甚至都不需要每天浇水。",en:"This flower is so hardcore that it doesn\'t need to be watered every day."};
descriptions["9271"]={cn:"随意种下的兰花种子，不知不觉间，你会发现你已经置身兰花盛开的天堂中了。",en:"Plant this seed and before you know it you\'ll find yourself surrounded by a beautiful Orchid paradise."};
descriptions["9272"]={cn:"收录于著名的《旅行者传送指南》丛书中。",en:"This is from the famous \"Zaapackers guide...\" collection."};
descriptions["9273"]={cn:"因为一直被模仿，红牛最后决定用法杖去打敌人的脸。",en:"After being mocked for years for using his cards in combat, Hon shut his opponent\'s faces with this long bat."};
