descriptions["9298"]={cn:"虽然你感觉鞋里闷热得像烤炉，但是柔软潮湿的靴子内衬让足部皮肤全天保持滋润。",en:"Even though you might feel like you\'re walking on flan, the supple and humid texture of these boots will keep your skin feeling well-hydrated all day long."};
descriptions["9299"]={cn:"把皇家豆芙毛插在皇家便便上，经过若干工序，制成了这双皮靴。十分高档。",en:"These boots are made by sticking royal feathers to royal guano. Very classy."};
descriptions["9303"]={cn:"在某些国家，藤壶木屐被用作一种侮辱性的道具来挑起决斗。",en:"In certain areas of the world, Barnacle Getas are thrown down to provoke duels."};
descriptions["9304"]={cn:"美观的腰带，让你看起来十分犀利。除非你是个骑士。",en:"This magnificent belt will make you look super sharp. Unless you\'re a Iop, of course."};
descriptions["9305"]={cn:"放暑假时，这条软木腰带折叠起来可以当安全带用。",en:"This wooden belt was designed to double up as a lifebelt during the summer holidays."};
descriptions["9310"]={cn:"没人告诉你，你有一颗金子般的心吗？",en:"Anyone ever told you that you\'ve got a heart of gold?"};
descriptions["9311"]={cn:"不值一提的包。容量庞大，可以让你随身携带一切你需要带的东西。",en:"This large bag might not be much to write home about. However, all you have to do is put things in it and you can take them with you anywhere!"};
descriptions["9312"]={cn:"吞噬你放进去的每一枚卡玛。一定是宝藏猎人发明的。",en:"This bag bites and steals any kamas you put inside it. It must have been invented by an Enutrof."};
descriptions["9313"]={cn:"并不是很高档的包。但是可以装下所有你需要的东西。",en:"This large bag might not be much to write home about. However, all you have to do is put things in it and you can take them with you anywhere!"};
descriptions["9315"]={cn:"不值一提的包。容量庞大，可以让你随身携带一切你需要带的东西。",en:"This large bag might not be much to write home about. However, all you have to do is put things in it and you can take them with you anywhere!"};
descriptions["9316"]={cn:"并不是很高档的包。但是可以装下所有你需要的东西。",en:"This large bag might not be much to write home about. However, all you have to do is put things in it and you can take them with you anywhere!"};
descriptions["9317"]={cn:"滑板初学者的理想选择。",en:"This cloak is ideal for learning to skateboard."};
descriptions["9318"]={cn:"玛尔布姐姐曾经用来包裹天上掉下来的七颗水晶球。结果她没有遇到长着尾巴的少年，多么完美的结局。",en:"A certain Mulba used this item to carry heavy items with her on her long, difficult quest to find the Seven Crystal Hens which fell from the stars."};
descriptions["9319"]={cn:"现在你拥有了啾啾的皇室证明，你只需要让所有的啾啾统统为你献身就可以了。",en:"Now you\'ve been royally tufted, all you have to do is convince the other Piwis to go and die alone."};
descriptions["9320"]={cn:"奇怪的披风，丑陋的外表是它力量的源泉。越脏，就越有用。",en:"This strange cape draws all its power from its dilapidated appearance. The dirtier it is, the more use it will be to you."};
descriptions["9321"]={cn:"这件披风散发着一股刺鼻的气味。其实只是多种怪物毛皮的混合物而已。",en:"Fair enough, this cloak has a very strong and unpleasant odor. It\'s basically a mix of various monster furs."};
descriptions["9322"]={cn:"这件披风散发着一股刺鼻的气味。其实只是多种怪物毛皮的混合物而已。",en:"Fair enough, this cloak has a very strong and unpleasant odor. It\'s basically a mix of various monster furs."};
descriptions["9323"]={cn:"这件披风散发着一股刺鼻的气味。其实只是多种怪物毛皮的混合物而已。",en:"Fair enough, this cloak has a very strong and unpleasant odor. It\'s basically a mix of various monster furs."};
descriptions["9324"]={cn:"这件披风散发着一股刺鼻的气味。其实只是多种怪物毛皮的混合物而已。",en:"Fair enough, this cloak has a very strong and unpleasant odor. It\'s basically a mix of various monster furs."};
descriptions["9330"]={cn:"披风上的优质毛皮能让主人在地底行动自如。好吧，也许不是，只是在空气中行动自如...",en:"The fur covering this cloak enables the wearer to move through earth faster. Okay, maybe not, but through the air it works..."};
descriptions["9332"]={cn:"这件披风是外太空的产物，看上去和你的羊绒渔网袜的颜色很相似。",en:"This cape is not from our galaxy, yet it seems similar in color to your Gobball wool fishnet stockings."};
descriptions["9337"]={cn:"风靡一时的帽子，现在看来丑得像恐龙。",en:"This headgear was very fashionable in days gone by, but these days you\'ll just look like a dinosaur wearing it."};
descriptions["9338"]={cn:"制作精良的指针，为新手精心打造。",en:"A well-forged clock hand, particularly suitable for novices."};
descriptions["9339"]={cn:"传说在午夜十二点刚过的时候使用，这把指针能将龙鸟车变成南瓜。",en:"Legend has it that this hand also has the power to turn Dragoturkeys into pumpkins if the bearer sits on one after the twelfth strike of midnight."};
descriptions["9342"]={cn:"现在你可以走进银行，玩卡玛卡玛变色龙游戏！",en:"Now you can go to the bank and play at...  Kama kama kama kama kama chameleons!"};
descriptions["9343"]={cn:"时间法师使用指针来鼓舞队友，给敌人致命一击。",en:"Acu the Xelor knew how to use his clock hands to awaken his friends\' senses as well as make his enemies suffer excruciating pain."};
descriptions["9345"]={cn:"让你更有男人味！你想多了。它只会让你更无趣。",en:"This amulet will make you a man. No, just kidding. It will just make you incredibly boring."};
descriptions["9346"]={cn:"骸骨士兵总是带着骷髅护符上阵，天知道这些骷髅是哪里来的...",en:"The Chafer always keeps an amulet made from the skull of one of his cousins on him. The weird thing is, the Chafer doesn\'t have any relations..."};
descriptions["9347"]={cn:"小巧可爱，舒适贴身。",en:"Nice and cute, this amulet will bring you a lot of comfort."};
descriptions["9348"]={cn:"据说在箭矢的降落点，你会发现宝藏。奇怪的是，只有当雨后天晴的时候才会出现。",en:"They say that, if you can find where your arrows have landed, it will lead you to a treasure. Strangely, this only seems to work when rain and rays of sunshine mix together."};
descriptions["9349"]={cn:"调校完美的强弓，射出的箭矢直击隐蔽敌人。怪物如惊弓之鸟，四散奔逃。",en:"Yamato\'s Rope has made more than one monster\'s heart beat a little faster. A finely tuned weapon, it can direct arrows to even the most well-hidden targets."};
descriptions["9352"]={cn:"这只崭新的护符看起来很重，一不小心就会踩穿地板。",en:"Your new amulet is so fat that when you put it on, you\'re in the basement surrounded by shards of wood."};
descriptions["9353"]={cn:"由树木和金属制成。让敌人尝尝你的厉害吧。",en:"This pendant is made from wood and metal fused together. That will really show your enemies what you\'re made of."};
descriptions["9354"]={cn:"由治愈者梅·多潘制造，可以扭转时间来阻止战斗。通常在结束战斗的时候会被插在恶魔的眼睛里。",en:"Made by the Eniripsa, Mie Dopan, this wand is able to turn back time to prevent fights. It normally ends up shoved in some demon\'s eye."};
descriptions["9355"]={cn:"你发现这件护符很烦人，因为上面的触须不停地挠你的胸脯。",en:"Wearers usually find this necklace really irritating, thanks to its decorative moustaches which tend to tickle the chest."};
descriptions["9356"]={cn:"据占星学家，本丹骑士的研究，天上的星星是由面包屑和果酱做成的。",en:"\"Did you know? The stars are actually a subtle mixture of fairy dust and custard!\"\n- Mye Iopik, astrologer"};
descriptions["9359"]={cn:"用途十分有限，最好还是拿来当痒痒挠。",en:"Given its limited capabilities, you\'d probably be better off using this wand as a back scratcher."};
descriptions["9362"]={cn:"经过烘培，还是不能食用。发酵粉的气味说不定会吸引来饥饿的骑士。",en:"Just because it was cooked in a bread oven, that doesn\'t mean this wand\'s edible. The lingering odor of baking powder will fool the hungriest Iops, though."};
descriptions["9368"]={cn:"构造简单，完全不是什么高档货。",en:"Fairly basic staff, not the stuff of legends."};
descriptions["9369"]={cn:"即将踏上远征路途的冒险者会带着伙伴的法杖上路。觉得孤单寂寞的时候就掏出来看看。",en:"Adventurers setting off on a long journey always take their partner\'s staff with them. Probably to make sure they have some company out there all alone."};
descriptions["9370"]={cn:"千里迢迢背井离乡来到此地的食人杖，十分怀念故土。带着法杖登上高山，插茱萸一株，这样做能激发它的潜能。",en:"Far from its Caniball, this exotic staff can feel quite homesick. That\'s why it\'s advisable to fight facing the sea, underneath a palm tree, to get the best out of it."};
descriptions["9371"]={cn:"很久以前，亚里士德将这枚戒指传给了一只聪明的幸运猫，伊斯多尔，他拥有无与伦比的敏捷动作。",en:"A long time ago, King Allister gave this ring to Isidor, a smart cat, renowned for his incomparable agility."};
descriptions["9375"]={cn:"能让佩戴者的存在感归零的戒指。不是隐形哦，真的不是隐形哦！",en:"This ring\'s strength lies in its ability to make its wearer completely transparent. You do understand we\'re not talking about invisibility here, don\'t you?"};
descriptions["9376"]={cn:"不要被朴素的外表迷惑了：它能驾驭好几群绵球。",en:"Don\'t be fooled by its simplistic appearance: this staff has already put more than one herd of Gobballs in its place."};
descriptions["9377"]={cn:"这把法杖由鲜活的树精根部制成。注意，这些树根会背叛他们的主人。",en:"This staff is made from living Treechnid roots. Be warned, these do have an annoying tendency to turn against their masters."};
descriptions["9380"]={cn:"如果使用太过频繁，会导致肌肉过度发达。",en:"Used too repetitively, this staff can lead to overdeveloped muscles."};
descriptions["9382"]={cn:"能提升使用者的力量。必要的时候，也可以当做食物。",en:"This club increases its bearer\'s power and can, if necessary, be eaten."};
descriptions["9383"]={cn:"武器的持有者操着一口极易分辨的典型阿玛克纳北方口音：跑！快跑！",en:"This weapon\'s owners can be easily recognized by their typical North Amakna accent and their battle cry, \"Pow! Right in\'t Kisser!\""};
descriptions["9384"]={cn:"让你看起来像个傻瓜，别说我没提醒过你！",en:"This weapon has the power to make you look a fool. Don\'t say we didn\'t warn you!"};
descriptions["9385"]={cn:"用于打劫土豪，搜刮他们的钱财。",en:"This club can be used to knock out the rich and pocket their valuables."};
descriptions["9386"]={cn:"前任主人丢掉了这根大棒，找了一根更新更美观的结实短棍代替。",en:"This bludgeon was probably betrayed by its owner for a better-looking, newer, more powerful club."};
descriptions["9392"]={cn:"十分精良的护肩。只是有一股刺鼻的绵球骚臭让你想吐。",en:"These could be quite classy, if only the nauseating odor they give off didn\'t make you want to vomit."};
descriptions["9393"]={cn:"质地坚韧，尼克·特普迫不及待地想拥有该种材料。",en:"As soft as they are firm, this is the sort of plastic Nick Tup would be dying to get his hands on."};
descriptions["9394"]={cn:"挖个坑，挖个小坑坑...挖到了卡玛真开心！",en:"Dig a little tunnel, dig a little tunnel... and always let your kamas be your guide!"};
descriptions["9398"]={cn:"谁能想到这世界上有这么大的变异虫？",en:"Who would have thought a Larva could be so big?"};
descriptions["9399"]={cn:"领子可收缩，让你可以更轻松地穿上胸甲。",en:"The collar of this particularly supple breastplate expands to let its owner put it on more easily."};
descriptions["9400"]={cn:"穿着总比什么都不穿好，至少这件破烂袍子能让你备受周围人的瞩目，和嘲笑。",en:"It might not be much good for anything else, but at least this deformed toga has the marvelous ability to make the people around you burst spontaneously into laughter."};
descriptions["9401"]={cn:"这件胸甲有些僵硬。为了回归自然，这是值得的代价。",en:"Yes, this breastplate might be a little stiff, but that\'s the price you have to pay if you want to be at one with nature."};
descriptions["9409"]={cn:"简易的斧子，不是什么高级货。",en:"This basic axe isn\'t really the stuff of legends."};
descriptions["9410"]={cn:"后现代艺术大斧，造型灵感来自于一本漫画。",en:"A postmodern axe based on a comic book."};
descriptions["9411"]={cn:"手头没有熊可斩的话，拿来切面包也挺好用的。",en:"If you don\'t have any bears to hand, this is just as useful for slicing your loaf."};
descriptions["9412"]={cn:"如果你觉得自己是个超级英雄，那么这把斧子会和你十分般配。现在你需要件多彩护甲来搭配。",en:"If you feel you\'re a superhero at heart, this axe is made for you. All you need now is an assortment of colored armor."};
descriptions["9413"]={cn:"并没有吞噬士兵，只是将他们轰杀成渣，但是看起来好像被恶魔吞噬了一样。",en:"This axe doesn\'t really eat militiamen. It does reduce them to mush though, which gives the impression that they\'ve been chewed."};
descriptions["9414"]={cn:"曾经属于著名的伐木工，布鲁斯·布尔古。当年他就是拿着这把斧子防身，晚上出门顺便砍掉一整片森林。",en:"An axe which used to belong to Brouce Boulgoure, the famous lumberjack. This weapon allowed him to defend himself when he went out to chop down whole forests at night."};
descriptions["9419"]={cn:"简易的锤子，不是什么高档货。",en:"This is just a basic hammer, not the stuff of legends."};
descriptions["9420"]={cn:"拿着这把锤子你就不由自主地想往敌人的脑袋上敲，汪汪汪。",en:"This mace will allow you to jump into things head first, without even thinking about it. A bit like before, really."};
descriptions["9421"]={cn:"传说这把锤子会偷偷溜走。你最好时刻紧握着它。",en:"Legend has it that this mace has a tendency to wander. We would, therefore, advise you to keep it firmly attached to your fist at all times to make sure you don\'t lose it."};
descriptions["9422"]={cn:"侧耳倾听，你会发现这把锤子始终在哼着一首曲子，余音在你的脑海里不停回荡。",en:"If you listen closely, you might notice that this mace is permanently whistling a little tune that gets stuck in your head."};
descriptions["9423"]={cn:"你喜欢动物？托罗也是。他毕生心血都交给了小动物。这把锤子代表了他和动物们的关系，脆弱得好似随时会被车辆碾死的跛脚绵球。",en:"So you like animals? So did Toh\'Lo. He devoted his whole life to them. This hammer kind of represents his relationship with animals, a communion as shaky as a lame Gobball on a freshly graveled driveway."};
descriptions["9424"]={cn:"兽人头目奥塔命令一群时间法师制造这把锤子，否则就杀掉整个村庄的居民。可是当他拿到完成品后，还是毁掉了整个村子。他只是想试试新武器的威力。",en:"Outar Great Bwork ordered these fearsome hammers from a village of Xelors with the promise of sparing the townspeople if the hammers were well made. When he received the hammers, he destroyed the village. He needed to try his new weapons after all."};
descriptions["9425"]={cn:"滑稽可笑的锤子，被敌人看到了，他们会捧腹大笑。这样一来就为你赢得了攻其不备的机会。笑到最后的会是你。",en:"This Hammer is so ridiculous that your enemy will burst out laughing the minute he sets eyes on you. The time gained by this diversion should let you have the last laugh, though."};
descriptions["9430"]={cn:"很普通的匕首，不是什么高档货。",en:"These aren\'t the best daggers in the World. They\'re certainly not the stuff of legends."};
descriptions["9431"]={cn:"精心打造的匕首，新手的理想选择。",en:"These well forged daggers are a good choice for novices."};
descriptions["9432"]={cn:"任何一个名符其实的宝藏猎人都留着满脸的胡子，老克里·诺希夫也不例外。有一天他的妻子，诺希夫太太为他买了一把剃须刀，他觉得还是拿来当作武器比较好...",en:"Any Enutrof worthy of the name has a beard, and old Krys Nosheive was no exception. One day his wife, Mrs Nosheive, bought him a razor, and he decided he would rather use it as a weapon..."};
descriptions["9433"]={cn:"由远古琥珀制成的匕首，在月亮岛荒芜之前，用于月亮岛的开垦。",en:"These daggers, forged from Ancestral Amber, were used in the colonization of Moon Island, before it became wild again."};
descriptions["9434"]={cn:"精良的小刀，曾经属于阿玛克纳的书记官佩恩。他用小刀在石头上做记录。",en:"These superb daggers used to belong to Penn the Amaknian scribe. He used them to engrave his stone notebooks."};
descriptions["9435"]={cn:"不要担心匕首从哪里飞来。它们实在是太滑了！",en:"Don\'t worry about where these daggers came from, or the fact that their handles seem to be a bit \"slippery\"!"};
descriptions["9436"]={cn:"根据欧几里德几何学，这是一个很标准的六面体，每一面都是正方形。呃，或许是长方形。又或者是别的什么...随便吧...有图有真相。",en:"If Euclidian geometry is to be believed, this crate is a prism of which all the faces are squares. Or rectangles. Or... whatever... You get the picture."};
descriptions["9438"]={cn:"漂亮的外表掩盖了刺鼻的臭气。在你脱下鞋子的时候，如果闻到臭气就可以赖在盆栽上。",en:"This delicate plant masks bad smells. It\'s perfect for when you take your Gobboots off."};
descriptions["9440"]={cn:"不想继续愚昧无知？你需要的是乱书堆，能为你的庇护袋营造出文化环境。你值得拥有！",en:"Sick of having to create your own disorder? What you need is the Pile of Books, which will mask your excessive tidiness of your abode. A must-have!"};
descriptions["9441"]={cn:"由蜘蛛腿和粗糙坚硬的毛皮制成。扫除刺鼻气味和污渍十分有用。",en:"Made from an Arachnee with a particularly rough and resistant skin, this brush is very useful for getting rid of bad smells and dirty marks."};
descriptions["9444"]={cn:"是的，嗯...红色的哦！",en:"Yes, ok... well you can\'t be good at everything!"};
descriptions["9445"]={cn:"也许是一个失落的弓手制造的，中间的红心比一般的靶子大了两倍。",en:"Probably made by a very frustrated Cra, the bull\'s eye at the center is considerably larger than usual."};
descriptions["9446"]={cn:"做工精良的宝剑，让你成为勇猛的斗士。敌人看到你就会落荒而逃。",en:"This Ha Sword, of the very best quality, will turn you into a valiant fighter. Just the sight of it sends even your most courageous enemies running for the hills."};
descriptions["9447"]={cn:"啊，那样更好...",en:"Ahh, that\'s better..."};
descriptions["9448"]={cn:"由动物骸骨、软骨和犄角制成的铁剑，锋利更胜幸运猫爪。更大更锋利。",en:"This curved blade, made from bone, cartilage and horn, is as sharp as an Ecaflip\'s claw. And a bit bigger and cleaner."};
descriptions["9449"]={cn:"看起来，熊猫武僧喝啤酒的速度远远超过酿酒的速度。",en:"Looks like the Pandawas are drinking the root beer faster than they can make it!"};
descriptions["9450"]={cn:"来自某个铁匠的店招...希望你的攻击招数能更强些。如果不能的话，你会倒大霉，除非你自己也开一家铁匠铺。",en:"This sword was taken from a Blacksmith\'s shop sign... Let\'s hope you\'ll be able to hit harder with it. If not, it\'s not going to be much good unless you open your own shop."};
descriptions["9451"]={cn:"容量大。但是你什么东西也不能放进去。",en:"This box has a very practical capacity. The problem is, you can\'t put anything in it."};
descriptions["9452"]={cn:"有人造谣说这道菜是用狗做的...",en:"Some people spread the unpleasant rumor that this dish is made from Bow Wows..."};
descriptions["9455"]={cn:"和你想的正相反，这只凳子上一个螺栓都没拧紧，所以，别坐。",en:"Since you got this stool, its design has been upgraded to better fit your curvaceous behind. If you plan on sitting on it anytime soon, visit the appropriate workshop and follow the recipe to make the latest adjustments."};
descriptions["9456"]={cn:"简易的剑刃，完全不是什么高档货。",en:"Basic sword, not the stuff of legends."};
descriptions["9457"]={cn:"制作精良的巨剑，新手必备。",en:"A well forged sword, interesting for beginners."};
descriptions["9458"]={cn:"曾经属于屠夫梅茨格，他切骨头的时候用的就是这把刀。一个骸骨士兵从他那里偷到了这把刀。从那以后，刀下断肢者层出不穷。",en:"This Blade once belonged to Metzger the Butcher, who used it to cut up bones. A Chafer managed to steal it from him and, in his hands, the blade has been responsible for numerous amputations."};
descriptions["9459"]={cn:"曾浸泡于狼的泪水中。勇士们坚信这样做能在战场上鼓舞士气，好运连连。",en:"This blade has bathed in the tears of a Boowolf. Lots of warriors think this brings luck and courage on the battlefield."};
descriptions["9460"]={cn:"古尔塔之剑在龙猪血中浸泡多时。任何能忍受这柄剑散发出的刺鼻气味的英雄都将有权使用这柄利剑。",en:"The Goultard was soaked in a Dragon Pig\'s blood. Any hero who can bear the stench given off by the sword will have earnt the right to use it in battle."};
descriptions["9463"]={cn:"真正的灌木，看起来像...假的。",en:"A real shrub that looks... Fake."};
descriptions["9464"]={cn:"对于任何幽灵派对来说，都是深受欢迎的佳酿。可是他们已经死了，所以只能看不能喝。",en:"This is a welcome addition to any Ghostof party. And since they\'re dead, they don\'t do much else."};
descriptions["9465"]={cn:"这张桌子上插了一把剑。这倒不是某次决斗的鉴证，怎么说呢，它可以看作是桌子的另一条腿，这样能让桌子更稳当点。这就是典型的伊欧普思维。",en:"The sword planted in this bent table is not the remains of some badly turned duel. No, it\'s kind of like a fourth leg. You know, to stabilize it. That\'s Iop thinking, that is."};
descriptions["9466"]={cn:"做工精良的铲子。新手入门专用。",en:"This shovel is well-made. It\'s an interesting weapon for beginners."};
descriptions["9467"]={cn:"有了这把铲子，你不仅可以收割自己的雏菊，还可以把敌人逼进死角。",en:"With this shovel, you won\'t just be able weed your own daisies, you can make sure your enemies push up theirs as well."};
descriptions["9468"]={cn:"用于铲除野草。由于功效出众，慢慢变成了军用品。",en:"This garden shovel is used to cut the rhizomes of weeds. It\'s also an excellent weapon when it comes to cutting other things."};
descriptions["9470"]={cn:"产自东方的铲子。始终浸泡在牛奶中，散发着一股宜人的香气。",en:"A good shovel from the east. Its made from Moogrr milk, which explains its rather delicate perfume."};
descriptions["9471"]={cn:"对于宝藏猎人来说，这把铲子不仅仅可以用来摘果子，更是一把强大的武器。",en:"This shovel isn\'t just used by Enutrofs to harvest fruit from their trees, but also as a formidable weapon."};
descriptions["9477"]={cn:"除了能让女孩子对你敬而远之以外，就只能遮风避雨了。",en:"Aside from making the ladies run away, this hat is pretty good against rain."};
descriptions["9478"]={cn:"这一定是你戴过的最烂的头盔了：头皮被尖锐的猪鬓戳刺撕扯着，还散发着一股猪骚味。",en:"This must surely be the worst hat you\'ve ever had to wear: it pricks, scratches and overpowers you with the smell of Blibli breath."};
descriptions["9479"]={cn:"轻如羽翼。你只需要等梦想照进现实的一天就好了...哦哒哒哒...",en:"This helmet is as light as a feather. All you have to do is wait for the wind to get up to turn your dreams of flying into reality... Crash Bang Wallop *stars*... Maybe not."};
descriptions["9480"]={cn:"让你看起来像紫色战士，恐虫战队的成员之一。",en:"This hat will make you look like the Purple Power Larva, the famous masked justice fighter from Bonta."};
descriptions["9481"]={cn:"一点也不适合你的木鱼脑袋。当然也不适合骑士的脑袋！",en:"This helmet doesn\'t fit your small head at all. Or even a Iop\'s, come to think of it!"};
descriptions["9483"]={cn:"不要跳太高，否则会一不小心卡在树枝上。还有更糟的，比如角上叉了两只咕咕尸体。",en:"Try not to jump in head first or you might end up stuck in a branch or, even worse, with a load of dead Piwis skewered on your helmet."};
descriptions["9485"]={cn:"现在你终于做好准备像个真正的士兵一样打仗了。好了，向前爬...呃，我是说向前冲！",en:"You\'re finally ready to fight like a true soldier. Crawl Out! erm, I mean FALL out!"};
descriptions["9486"]={cn:"全世界女士最爱。她们喜欢带这款软帽参加南瓜节庆典。要小心粘在你头上的蜘蛛网了，一旦黏住就很难脱落。",en:"This helmet is favored by ladies all over the World to celebrate Al Howin\'s Day in style. Please note that the Arachnee web sticks to your hair and can be quite difficult to get out."};
descriptions["9487"]={cn:"简易的软靴。刚启程的年轻冒险者的理想选择。",en:"Very basic boots which are ideal for young adventurers just setting off on their journey."};
descriptions["9488"]={cn:"适合在泥中奔走以及踩碎地板。别穿着它们去舞厅，那简直是谋杀。",en:"These boots are great for walking in mud and ruining floorboards. If you wear them on the dance floor, it will be murder."};
descriptions["9489"]={cn:"光鲜亮丽，展现着坚强的底蕴，这双皮靴是“皇家”的代名词。",en:"They shine; they exude strength; these boots are, in every way, royal."};
descriptions["9490"]={cn:"外硬内柔，战斗时柔软的内衬会不断挠你的脚趾。",en:"Hard on the outside, their inside is lightly quilted with a soft lining that will tickle your toes while you\'re kicking butt."};
descriptions["9491"]={cn:"虽然晚上穿出去很帅气，脱下来的时候却很痛苦，靴子已经紧紧黏在你腿上了。",en:"However good an impression these boots make on a night out, they\'re a real pain to get off once they\'ve stuck to your legs."};
descriptions["9492"]={cn:"好看但不实用。这件披风对于年轻的勇士仍然有诱惑力。",en:"Classy, but not very useful. This cape will still have a knockout effect on young warriors."};
descriptions["9493"]={cn:"让你精神饱满，这是它唯一的优点。天知道穿着它的人是怎样才忍住瘙痒的。",en:"This mass of Blibli fur makes its wearer more vigorous, which is important since no one knows how they manage to bear the tickling that long."};
descriptions["9494"]={cn:"比豆芙披风少用一点毛皮，但是手感却柔顺十倍。就是这么自信！",en:"Less fur than the Tofu cloak, but ten times silkier. That\'s Royalty for you!"};
descriptions["9495"]={cn:"皇家绵球副官的披风，看起来非常强力有型。",en:"This cloak, worn by his great Royal Gobball Associate, is both incredibly stylish and incredibly powerful."};
descriptions["9497"]={cn:"看起来优雅端庄，但是却能轻易黏住乱飞的苍蝇。买披风易，藏披风难。",en:"This cloak may start off as the very picture of elegance, but it collects flies like nobody\'s business, so keeping it that way might be more of a challenge than even you bargained for."};
descriptions["9498"]={cn:"新手的好伙伴。",en:"A little belt for budding adventurers."};
descriptions["9499"]={cn:"坚实强韧。虽然不太美观，但是能让你足够强硬。",en:"Very sturdy and resistant, this belt will make you powerful, if not graceful."};
descriptions["9500"]={cn:"看来是我高估你了。哦哒，哦哒哒哒。",en:"Hitting with your bare hands is overrated. Awkkkkkk ooooff cr-r-a-a-ck clunk-eth."};
descriptions["9501"]={cn:"这条名贵的腰带上甚至还装着一个播种器！",en:"For once, you\'ve got your hands on a really classy belt. It even has an integrated seed dispenser."};
descriptions["9502"]={cn:"上面的小蜘蛛，让你免受腰部以下部位的攻击。",en:"The little Arachnee on the front of this belt will protect you from any low blows."};
descriptions["9503"]={cn:"散发着一股熟悉的刺鼻气息，不同点是更臭更熏人...",en:"These Epaulettes have the familiar scent of Gobballs, but much stronger and more pungent."};
descriptions["9504"]={cn:"这对护肩让你看起来不像是个勇者，倒像是个小丑。",en:"All we can say about these epaulettes is that they\'ll make you look more like a crowd entertainer than a brave warrior."};
descriptions["9505"]={cn:"为什么不穿上和朋友们跳支舞呢？",en:"Why not take these on a whirl with your friends?"};
descriptions["9506"]={cn:"哦哒哒哒哒哒哒哒哒！！！",en:"A lightly perfumed breastplate which is wonderfully attractive to hungry Gobballs in the area."};
descriptions["9507"]={cn:"第一眼看上去觉得这件胸甲很不起眼。实际上，它比其他胸甲更加肮脏。这一定是皇家绵球多年智慧的积累。",en:"At first glance, there\'s nothing royal about this breastplate. In fact, it\'s even mangier and dirtier than the rest. That must be proof of the years of wisdom acquired by the Royal Gobball."};
descriptions["9508"]={cn:"由旋鸟背部的皮毛制成，松软有弹性，保护你在正面对敌时，不受伤害。",en:"This breastplate, which is supposed to protect the front of your body, was, in fact, made with a Whirly\'s backside, which is softer and more elastic.\n"};
descriptions["9509"]={cn:"这是个对于新手十分有用的戒指，小孩子和幸运猫的最爱。",en:"This is a lovely little ring for beginners and which will be cherished by kids and Ecaflips alike."};
descriptions["9511"]={cn:"小小的死蜘蛛头好像在嘲笑你，快用武器碾碎它！",en:"The small, dead Arachnee head which smiles at you from this ring seems to be taunting you: crushing it with your weapon wiped the smirk off its face though, didn\'t it?"};
descriptions["9512"]={cn:"等级不高，也不实用。集齐套装的时候会很厉害。",en:"Not very classy, not very useful, but nice when you have the set."};
descriptions["9513"]={cn:"点击两下来把旧物品转换成相同类型的新物品。",en:"Double-click to transform your old item into a new one of the same type."};
