descriptions["9519"]={cn:"千里迢迢背井离乡来到此地的食人杖，十分怀念故土。带着法杖登上高山，插茱萸一株，这样做能激发它的潜能。",en:"Far from its Kanniball, this exotic staff can feel quite homesick. That\'s why it\'s advisable to fight facing the sea, underneath a palm tree, to get the best out of it."};
