descriptions["9531"]={cn:"很久以前，亚里士德将这枚戒指传给了一只聪明的幸运猫，伊斯多尔，他拥有无与伦比的敏捷动作。",en:"A long time ago, King Allister gave this ring to Isidor, a smart cat, renowned for his incomparable agility."};
descriptions["9532"]={cn:"很久以前，亚里士德将这枚戒指传给了一只聪明的幸运猫，伊斯多尔，他拥有无与伦比的敏捷动作。",en:"A long time ago, King Allister gave this ring to Isidor, a smart cat, renowned for his incomparable agility."};
descriptions["9533"]={cn:"很久以前，亚里士德将这枚戒指传给了一只聪明的幸运猫，伊斯多尔，他拥有无与伦比的敏捷动作。",en:"A long time ago, King Allister gave this ring to Isidor, a smart cat, renowned for his incomparable agility."};
descriptions["9537"]={cn:"经过烘培，还是不能食用。发酵粉的气味说不定会吸引来饥饿的骑士。",en:"Just because it was cooked in a bread oven, that doesn\'t mean this wand\'s edible. The lingering odor of baking powder will fool the hungriest Iops, though."};
descriptions["9538"]={cn:"经过烘培，还是不能食用。发酵粉的气味说不定会吸引来饥饿的骑士。",en:"Just because it was cooked in a bread oven, that doesn\'t mean this wand\'s edible. The lingering odor of baking powder will fool the hungriest Iops, though."};
