descriptions["9542"]={cn:"点击两下来把旧物品转换成相同类型的新物品。",en:"Double-click to transform your old item into a new one of the same type."};
descriptions["9549"]={cn:"似乎能让拥有者微笑应对任何情况。如果你确定想拥有它，你得确保一天刷两次牙！",en:"It seems this terrible helmet enables its wearer to smile in all situations.  If you want one of these, you\'re going to have to make sure you brush your teeth twice a day!"};
descriptions["9550"]={cn:"外表是会欺骗人的，相信你自己对于气味的感觉：永远不要去想这根羽毛是从哪个部位拔下来的。",en:"Appearances can be deceptive, trust your sense of smell: it\'s probably better you don\'t know which end of the Piwi this immaculate feather was pulled from."};
descriptions["9551"]={cn:"皇家啾啾的脚很大，导致这双拖鞋也很大。疲惫双脚的良好选择。",en:"The Royal Piwi has rather fat ankles, so these slippers make comfortable boots for tired feet."};
descriptions["9552"]={cn:"不仅仅是一堆羽毛。是一堆皇家羽毛！",en:"This belt is much more than a pile of feathers. It\'s a pile of royal feathers!"};
descriptions["9554"]={cn:"“一个戒指，哦哒。两个戒指，哦哒哒！”\n诺斯特拉诺斯 - 随想录",en:"\"One ring, biff kapow. Two rings, biff bang kablooey!\"\nNostralanus - Thoughts"};
descriptions["9555"]={cn:"哦哒哒哒哒哒哒哒哒！",en:"The Kapowmulet? There\'s nothing better for pow whap thwack biff bap bap zwapp sploosh klonk blurp ker-plopping all day long!"};
descriptions["9556"]={cn:"全能的腰带。好吧，几乎全能。哦哒哒哒！",en:"This belt does everything. Well, almost. Kapow sock whack!"};
descriptions["9557"]={cn:"床单上发现了四条滋滋腿！昨晚发生了什么事情？",en:"Four Moskito Paws! Now there\'s something that will make a nice addition to your collection!"};
descriptions["9558"]={cn:"罕见的触角，一直散发着创生力量。",en:"This rare horn is still bursting with Wakfu."};
descriptions["9560"]={cn:"战斗奖励。\n庇护袋装饰品。",en:"Fight Bonus."};
descriptions["9561"]={cn:"期待你的第一桶金，卡玛卡玛卡玛卡玛！",en:"Here\'s what you need to start a merchant career. Give me the kamas!"};
descriptions["9563"]={cn:"据说皮皮尾巴能为爱情带来好运。有多走运取决于尾巴的大小。",en:"Prespic Tails are highly sought-after for their legendary ability to bring luck to their love conquests. The amount of luck is directly proportional to their size."};
descriptions["9564"]={cn:"如果你在寻找装扮成巫喵王的服饰，千万别选这件。除非你想扮成长毛的愤怒造型。",en:"If you were looking for a wig for a Rigide Barjo costume, you might not want to choose this one. Unless you\'re looking for the fiery, hairy, flea-infested version, of course."};
descriptions["9565"]={cn:"无论你是要牙签还是要一个新箭头，尖刺都是你最好的选择。",en:"Whether you want a toothpick or a new arrow head, there\'s nothing better than a Prespic Peak."};
descriptions["9566"]={cn:"拥有如此锋利的兽爪，为什么皮皮还是很脆弱？真搞不懂。",en:"How does a Prespic manage to be so agile with those two unfortunate toes on his paws? It\'s a mystery."};
descriptions["9567"]={cn:"战斗必备护具。能吸收并反弹任何攻击，保护你尊贵的屁股不受伤害。。",en:"Don\'t worry about going into battle. This thick cloak will absorb any hits on behalf of your precious butt, whilst, at the same time, injuring your opponent."};
descriptions["9568"]={cn:"由沙皇滋滋的两片翅膀制成。用于把自己打扮成治愈者。",en:"Made from Tsar Tsu Tsu\'s two wings, this cloak is perfect for disguising yourself as an Eniripsa."};
descriptions["9569"]={cn:"相比起大多数冒险者穿的朴素的深色调鞋子，这双靴子神气多了。",en:"These elegant boots with liven up the dull and dark colors worn by most adventurers."};
descriptions["9570"]={cn:"如果我是你，我绝不会用手摸头发！",en:"I wouldn\'t run my hands through my hair, if I were you!"};
descriptions["9571"]={cn:"由一堆尖刺制成的腰带，可以抵御任何外界压力。然而，一旦穿上之后，会很难卸下。别说我没警告过你...",en:"This belt, made from woven spikes, can withstand any amount of pressure. However, once you\'ve got it on, it\'s quite delicate to remove. Don\'t say we didn\'t warn you..."};
descriptions["9573"]={cn:"只需轻轻一咬，就能撕碎你的牙齿：女士们，早就提醒过你们不要接近大灰狼了！",en:"This delicate breastplate can tear your teeth apart with one single bite: ladies, you have been warned what will happen if you get too close to the big bad Boowolf."};
descriptions["9574"]={cn:"你应该避免耸肩等剧烈运动，否则人们会以为你被一堆滋滋正面袭击了。",en:"You should avoid making any sudden movements when you\'ve got these equipped, or people might assume you walked face first into a swarm of Moskitos."};
descriptions["9575"]={cn:"战斗奖励。\n庇护袋装饰品。",en:"Fight Bonus."};
descriptions["9578"]={cn:"没有什么比一杯苏打水更提神的了！",en:"Nothing like a nice cool root beer on a sunny afternoon to forget your latest heartbreak!"};
descriptions["9595"]={cn:"防水效果一般，但是能帮助你在矿难发生的时候逃命。",en:"These boots are no use in the rain, but they will help you run away if a mine starts collapsing above your head."};
descriptions["9600"]={cn:"哞哞身上最好吃最柔嫩的肉...",en:"This cut was taken from the heart, the softest and tenderest part of the Moogrr..."};
descriptions["9602"]={cn:"经过深入广泛的研究，发现哞哞原来是用脖子上的铃铛互相交谈的。也许这是唯一能让骑士明白的沟通方式。",en:"After extended research on the subject, it has been discovered that Moogrrs use these bells to talk to one another. M aybe this could finally be a method of communication Iops understand?"};
descriptions["9604"]={cn:"让你成为英雄的宝剑！剑身沉重，仅仅是携带着它都能锻炼你的肌肉。剑体修长，你不得不举着它行走。",en:"A sword to make a hero of you! It\'s so heavy that you\'ll get muscular just carrying it, and so long that you\'ll need to walk tall to keep it off the ground."};
descriptions["9605"]={cn:"时间法师使用指针来鼓舞队友，给敌人致命一击。",en:"Acu the Xelor knew how to use his clock hands to awaken his friends\' senses as well as make his enemies suffer excruciating pain."};
