descriptions["9613"]={cn:"奇怪的金属昆虫，已经破破烂烂。",en:"A strange, half-broken, metallic insect."};
descriptions["9614"]={cn:"上面到底写了些什么阴谋诡计？",en:"What could these diabolically written plans possibly be for?"};
descriptions["9615"]={cn:"多亏了这对肩甲，你能将正义的种子散播到贫瘠的地区。或者你也可以变成一个不断追求力量的疯子，满脑子想着自私自利的正义。",en:"Thanks to these epaulettes, you can spread justice to the impoverished. Or you can become a power-thirsty lunatic with his own selfish ideas about justice."};
descriptions["9616"]={cn:"你必须流利地念“黑化肥会挥发”十遍而且舌头不打结才能穿上这件胸甲。",en:"Before you wear this armor, there is one condition: you have to be able to say \"Sue shooed Shushus by the seashore\" without getting your tongue twisted."};
descriptions["9618"]={cn:"由萨弗基亚聪明的鱼贩发明，用腐败的肉汤的臭味掩盖死鱼的腥味。",en:"This stew was invented by Sufokia\'s ingenious fishmongers, who found out they could conceal the stench of rotten fish with the even stronger smell of a sour broth."};
descriptions["9619"]={cn:"让你看起来像是阿玛克纳的正直国民。",en:"When used alongside other items, the Amaknian Amulet will make you into an \'honest\' citizen of the Nation of Amakna."};
descriptions["9620"]={cn:"让你看起来像阿玛克纳的正直国民。",en:"When used alongside other items, the Amaknian Ring will make you into an \'honest\' citizen of the Nation of Amakna."};
descriptions["9621"]={cn:"让你看起来像是阿玛克纳的正直国民。",en:"When used alongside other items, the Amaknian Cloak will make you into an \'honest\' citizen of the Nation of Amakna."};
descriptions["9622"]={cn:"让你看起来像是阿玛克纳的正直国民。",en:"When used alongside other items, these Amaknian Boots will make you into an \'honest\' citizen of the Nation of Amakna."};
descriptions["9624"]={cn:"它深知如何取悦私奔的情人。离乡的忧虑，以及成百上千条锦囊妙计，在你发觉之前，它已经帮你打点好一切。",en:"This bow knows how to satisfy lovers of breakouts. A hint of nostalgia and a ton of good ideas, and, before you know it, the flood gates have opened."};
descriptions["9625"]={cn:"缩水版的斧子，就像它的前主人一样。别想了，年轻人...正版货十个人都搬不动。",en:"Just like its ex-owner, this is a scaled-down version. Don\'t even think about it, pipsqueak - even ten of you couldn\'t lift the original."};
descriptions["9626"]={cn:"这把钩刀不是为了香蕉船而造的，也不是昨天造的！",en:"This Billhook was not created on a banana boat. Nor was it made yesterday!"};
descriptions["9627"]={cn:"所有人都爱发牢骚...但不是所有人都爱疯兔！",en:"Everyone likes Grumbler. especially as a protective wristband!"};
descriptions["9628"]={cn:"让你看起来很有品味！没其他用处！",en:"Giving you some class is what this amulet does best! And it doesn\'t do much else!"};
descriptions["9629"]={cn:"基于野蛮人库南曾经用过的一把刀制作而成。",en:"This cutlass is based on the one used by Coonan the Beastbarian."};
descriptions["9630"]={cn:"如果你想舒缓你内心的渴望，那么最好不要用这柄镰刀。",en:"Equipping this tool/weapon can lead to disturbing hallucinations, although some find it very pleasant and eye-opening."};
descriptions["9636"]={cn:"贵族游戏，但是五分钟后你就觉得无聊了，你开始想象你的下一根棍子是什么样的。",en:"Fun for the novelty, but after five minutes it gets boring and you start dreaming of your next club."};
descriptions["9637"]={cn:"你值得拥有。",en:"Because you\'re worth... something. Maybe."};
descriptions["9638"]={cn:"历经沧桑的智慧指针，指引命运所在。",en:"The age-old wisdom of this clock hand will guide you to your destiny."};
descriptions["9639"]={cn:"独特的箭矢发射系统，使其名扬四海。",en:"This bow is famous for its one-of-a-kind arrow propulsion system."};
descriptions["9640"]={cn:"可以窃取魔族灵魂碎片的法杖。不过，这只是一件便宜的赝品。",en:"The Tumboler Staff was a weapon capable of stealing pieces of Shushu souls. Unfortunately, this Tumboler Staff is just a cheap replica."};
descriptions["9641"]={cn:"制作精良的鳄骨匕首，你值得拥有。",en:"An extremely well-forged dagger, this weapon will make a worthy adversary of you."};
descriptions["9642"]={cn:"临阵对敌十分有效，但是你很难找到一种佩戴它的办法...",en:"This claymore is terribly efficient. All you have to do is figure out the best place to stick it..."};
descriptions["9643"]={cn:"令人难以忘却的斧子！敌人最好龟缩起来。只需对准头部的一击，就能让他们晕厥！",en:"What an impreschive axshe! Your opponent had better make himshelf schmall. It would only take one hit on the head to knock him out for the count!"};
descriptions["9644"]={cn:"这把魔杖是柔软又好用的完美典范！你的敌人即将长眠地下...",en:"Just because it\'s soft, doesn\'t mean it\'s useless. This wand is the perfect example of that! Your enemies will soon be in an eternal sleep..."};
descriptions["9645"]={cn:"献给真正的领导者。裁判加油！",en:"A hammer for a real leader."};
descriptions["9646"]={cn:"即便你浑身全是破布，这把铲子也能让你举止优雅。皇帝一向只穿新装！",en:"Even if you\'re dressed in rags, this shovel will make you seem elegant and refined. Whatever happened to calling a spade a spade?"};
descriptions["9647"]={cn:"能静下来享受轻松真是太棒了。远离一切大大小小的战争战役的烦恼，安乐、平静、无忧无虑...",en:"Ah, it\'s nice to calm and relaxed, tucked away from all the wars and the bloody battles, happy, unruffled, inoffensive..."};
descriptions["9648"]={cn:"无拘无束的披风，注定流浪一生。",en:"A free-thinking, radical cloak, destined for a bohemian lifestyle."};
descriptions["9649"]={cn:"鞋跟带有小刺，用来踢巨魔的屁股很好用。",en:"Equipped with little spikes at the heel, these boots are just the thing for kicking Trool butt."};
descriptions["9650"]={cn:"秋叶飘落的时候，你可以戴着这顶帽子躲在枯叶堆里吓人一跳。现代时尚总是令人吃惊...！",en:"When fall comes, you can hide malevolently in piles of dead leaves using this hat. Technology never ceases to amaze!"};
descriptions["9651"]={cn:"这个护符可以阻拦你的敌人。但是无法遮阳蔽日。",en:"This amulet may well protect you from enemies, but it can\'t protect you from the sun!"};
descriptions["9652"]={cn:"也许是唯一能让你在上面吃点心的护肩了...",en:"Probably the only epaulettes you can snack on..."};
descriptions["9653"]={cn:"卢克，我是你的...",en:"\"Luke, I am your...\""};
descriptions["9654"]={cn:"夕阳西下的时候，没有比弹一首曲子更惬意的了。",en:"At the crack of dawn, there\'s no sweeter sound than a lute ditty."};
descriptions["9655"]={cn:"轻易黏住狡猾的敌人。",en:"This shield is ideal for taking care of those slippery opponents."};
descriptions["9656"]={cn:"日记中的一页，记载着一个被遗忘的藏宝室，可以从哐哐矿洞进入。据说入口处用岩石伪装了起来。",en:"A page from a diary recounting the existence of a forgotten gallery accessible from the Mini-Mine. It says the entrance is camouflaged by rocks."};
descriptions["9660"]={cn:"让你看起来像是个邦塔的正直国民。",en:"When used alongside other items, the Bontarian Amulet will make you into an \'honest\' citizen of the Nation of Bonta."};
descriptions["9661"]={cn:"让你看起来像邦塔的正直国民。",en:"When used alongside other items, the Bontarian Ring will make you into an \'honest\' citizen of the Nation of Bonta."};
descriptions["9662"]={cn:"让你看起来像是邦塔的正直国民。",en:"When used alongside other items, the Bontarian Cloak will make you into an \'honest\' citizen of the Nation of Bonta."};
descriptions["9664"]={cn:"让你看起来像是邦塔的正直国民。",en:"When used alongside other items, these Bontarian Boots will make you into an \'honest\' citizen of the Nation of Bonta."};
descriptions["9665"]={cn:"想来个晒伤妆吗？",en:"Fancy getting a bit of a tan?"};
descriptions["9666"]={cn:"战斗奖励。\n庇护袋装饰品。",en:"Fight Bonus."};
descriptions["9667"]={cn:"这份文件允许你使用\"先贤\"称号，授予那些老一辈见证了世界变迁的人...",en:"This document permits you to use the title of \"Ancestral Elder,\" reserved for the oldies of tomorrow who have already seen their World evolve..."};
descriptions["9668"]={cn:"让你看起来像是个布拉克玛的正直国民。",en:"When used alongside other items, the Brakmarian Amulet will make you into an \'honest\' citizen of the Nation of Brakmar."};
descriptions["9669"]={cn:"让你看起来像布拉克玛的正直国民。",en:"When used alongside other items, this Brakmarian Ring will make you into an \'honest\' citizen of the Nation of Brakmar."};
descriptions["9670"]={cn:"让你看起来像是布拉克玛的正直国民。",en:"When used alongside other items, this Brakmarian Cloak will make you into an \'honest\' citizen of the Nation of Brakmar."};
descriptions["9672"]={cn:"和其它的物品一比，就让你看起来像是布拉克玛的正直国民。",en:"When used alongside other items, these Brakmarian Boots will make you into an \'honest\' citizen of the Nation of Brakmar."};
descriptions["9680"]={cn:"由干燥的树精灵木制成的拖鞋，十分舒适。木质的内衬，充满粘液，每一步都如履平地。",en:"These thongs, made from dried Treechnid wood, are surprisingly comfortable: the wooden sole is filled with sap that cushions your each and every step!"};
descriptions["9681"]={cn:"穿起披风，你看起来就和树皮一样粗糙。",en:"If you want to look gnarly, snap this cape up!"};
descriptions["9682"]={cn:"戴上之后，你就明白什么叫做敲木头，祈求好运不溜走了。",en:"That\'s what you call knocking on wood!"};
descriptions["9683"]={cn:"穿上它，告诉全世界你有多强力！",en:"With these on your shoulders, you\'ll be able to show the whole World what you\'re made of!"};
descriptions["9684"]={cn:"喝的时候捂住鼻子：并不仅仅是因为邦塔传统的缘故，而是喝下去后有一股淡淡的羊尿味...",en:"Hold your nose when drinking this: not only is it a Bontarian tradition, it also masks the aftertaste of Gobball-pee..."};
descriptions["9685"]={cn:"喝的时候捂住鼻子：并不仅仅是因为布拉克玛传统的缘故，而是喝下去后有一股淡淡的羊尿味...",en:"Hold your nose when drinking this: not only is it a Brakmarian tradition, it also masks the aftertaste of Tofu pee..."};
descriptions["9686"]={cn:"喝的时候捂住鼻子：并不仅仅是因为萨弗基亚传统的缘故，而是喝下去后有一股淡淡的羊尿味...",en:"Hold your nose when drinking this: not only is it a Sufokian tradition, it also masks the aftertaste of Larvae..."};
descriptions["9689"]={cn:"临时控制测试",en:"Temporary control test"};
descriptions["9690"]={cn:"夹得乐饮料，真正的骑士饮料！",en:"Gataurade For real Iops."};
descriptions["9691"]={cn:"三层者喱，一点点咖啡...开始新的一天吧！",en:"Three layers of jelly and a little pinch of coffee - that\'s the way to start the day!"};
descriptions["9692"]={cn:"在你一口一口咬下去的时候，会听到“哞哞”的叫声。",en:"Legend has it that, if this dish is cooked the French way, it will even moo as you gently devour it."};
descriptions["9694"]={cn:"据说咬一口可以带来财富和光荣。让我们看看人们现在是否仍然毫不犹豫地咬下去...",en:"It is said that a large bite into this rump brings riches and glory. Let\'s see if people still think twice about doing it now."};
descriptions["9696"]={cn:"勇敢地踏上著名探险家曾经走过的路途吧。",en:"Now you can set off to boldly go where the famous explorer has already gone."};
descriptions["9701"]={cn:"嗝出来舒服多了！",en:"Better out than in!"};
descriptions["9702"]={cn:"一只蓝色的豆芙？我已经几百年没见过了...",en:"A Blue Tofu? I haven\'t seen one of them in centuries..."};
descriptions["9703"]={cn:"宠物装备可以于宠物设定介面中更改。此物品已无用处，可以将其分解掉。",en:"Pet equipment can be changed in the pet settings interface. This item is obsolete; you can recycle it."};
descriptions["9704"]={cn:"想要告诉世界你站在哪一边？戴着它，所有人都能一目了然。\n你浑身散发着蓝色创生光环。",en:"Do you want to show the World whose team you\'re on? With this charm, it will be clear to everyone.\nSurrounds you with a bluish aura."};
descriptions["9705"]={cn:"天天都是圣巧克力节！",en:"For a successful St. Ballotwine!"};
descriptions["9706"]={cn:"想要告诉世界你站在哪一边？戴着它，所有人都一目了然。\n你浑身散发着紫色毁灭光环。",en:"Do you want to show the World whose team you\'re on? With this icon, it will be clear to everyone.\nSurrounds you with a purplish aura."};
descriptions["9707"]={cn:"这份文件允许你使用\"鉴定师\"称号，授予那些走过古老征程的人...",en:"This document permits you to use the title of \"Eliatrope Connoisseur,\" reserved for those who have lived ancient adventures..."};
descriptions["9708"]={cn:"宠物装备可以于宠物设定介面中更改。此物品已无用处，可以将其分解掉。",en:"Pet equipment can be changed in the pet settings interface. This item is obsolete; you can recycle it."};
descriptions["9709"]={cn:"可以请你跳支舞吗？来吧！",en:"Well, what are you waiting for? Dance!"};
descriptions["9710"]={cn:"从这颗小小的种子里，你可以种出充满创生能量的花朵。多么富有诗意...\n能种植于任何草地中。",en:"From this little seed, you can grow a Flower bursting with Wakfu. So poetic...\nCan be planted in any type of grass."};
descriptions["9711"]={cn:"放在庇护袋里，看起来就像充满消失秘宝的博物馆。",en:"Just what you need to make your Haven Bag or Haven World look like a museum full of forgotten treasures."};
descriptions["9712"]={cn:"放在庇护袋里，看起来就像充满消失秘宝的博物馆。",en:"Just what you need to make your Haven Bag or Haven World look like a museum full of forgotten treasures."};
descriptions["9713"]={cn:"庇护袋的华丽装饰品，它代表着远征的胜利。",en:"A beautiful decoration, representing a distant, collaborative success."};
descriptions["9714"]={cn:"漂亮的饰物，代表着遥远的成功。\n可以放在庇护袋的装饰屋里。",en:"A beautiful decoration, representing a distant success."};
descriptions["9719"]={cn:"树莓味，令你口气清新，越嚼越有味！",en:"This little Jelly is particularly nice to chew and is a wonderful breath freshener. Blue Raspberry flavor."};
descriptions["9720"]={cn:"薄荷味，令你口气清新，越嚼越有味！",en:"This little Jelly is particularly nice to chew and is a wonderful breath freshener. Mint flavor."};
descriptions["9721"]={cn:"草莓味，令你口气清新，越嚼越有味！",en:"This little Jelly is particularly nice to chew and is a wonderful breath freshener. Strawberry flavor."};
descriptions["9722"]={cn:"取自者喱皇帝的头部。简单来讲，就是皇家脑液。",en:"Royal Jelly is a secretion from King Jellix\'s cephalic glands. In short, it\'s a royal loogie."};
descriptions["9723"]={cn:"只有我，最摇摆！",en:"Gettin\' jiggly wit it!"};
descriptions["9724"]={cn:"和你的朋友们整夜狂欢吧！",en:"This will keep your friends on their toes all night long!"};
descriptions["9727"]={cn:"保护好自己的国家是你的唯一选择！",en:"Protecting your Nation is the only way of life!"};
descriptions["9728"]={cn:"穿上徽章，成为真正的士兵，时刻准备追缉逃犯。",en:"Wear this Insignia and you\'ll be a true soldier, ready to track down Outlaws like a pro."};
descriptions["9729"]={cn:"这本书包含了关于士兵的一切知识（也可以直接拿来往敌人头上砸）。",en:"All you need to know about the role of a soldier (can also be used to knock the enemy out)."};
descriptions["9730"]={cn:"醉心于煮面包吗（什么都能煮，别在意细节）？请用正确的方式穿上这件围裙，一秒变食神！",en:"Sick of burning bread (and everything else, for that matter)? Wear this apron right, and you\'ll be a top chef in no time!"};
descriptions["9731"]={cn:"这顶厨师帽没法让你成为厨房间的大神，不过至少能让你看起来像那么回事！",en:"This chef\'s hat might not turn you into a whiz in the kitchen, but at least you\'ll look the part!"};
descriptions["9734"]={cn:"是的，就是阿尔伯特传奇的炖肉，放在最后品尝。嗯嗯嗯！",en:"That\'s right, Alibert\'s legendary stew, yours to savor at last. Yum!"};
descriptions["9735"]={cn:"律令通行无阻。",en:"Law enforcement made easy."};
descriptions["9736"]={cn:"宠物装备可以于宠物设定介面中更改。此物品已无用处，可以将其分解掉。",en:"Pet equipment can be changed in the pet settings interface. This item is obsolete; you can recycle it."};
descriptions["9737"]={cn:"宠物装备可以于宠物设定介面中更改。此物品已无用处，可以将其分解掉。",en:"Pet equipment can be changed in the pet settings interface. This item is obsolete; you can recycle it."};
descriptions["9738"]={cn:"柠檬味，令你口气清新，越嚼越有味！",en:"This little Jelly is particularly nice to chew and is a wonderful breath freshener. Lemon flavor."};
descriptions["9739"]={cn:"新手用的披风。正好可以覆盖你的屁股，你还想怎么样？",en:"A nice cloak for beginners. It\'s just long enough to cover your butt, What more could you ask for?"};
descriptions["9744"]={cn:"和真正的老牌素食主义者不同，根据执政官的营养师最新推荐，你必须每天喝五瓶老酸奶才能保证营养平衡。",en:"Not as old-fashioned as real veggies, you have to eat five portions of veh cheese a day according to the latest recommendations from the governor\'s nutritionists."};
descriptions["9746"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["9747"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["9748"]={cn:"千万不要把药膏往脸上抹...刺激性强，易诱发黑头粉刺。\n提高畜牧业技能。",en:"Whatever you do, don\'t apply this balm to your face. It\'s an irritant and encourages blackheads.\nImproves trapper skills."};
descriptions["9749"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["9750"]={cn:"这种多用途面粉目前仅限于几种配方。预计很快会有所改善。",en:"This all-purpose flour is limited to a few recipes for the moment. An improvement is expected soon."};
descriptions["9752"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["9753"]={cn:"一个被牛头人无情践踏的苹朵？可悲，但是可口。",en:"An Api, heartlessly crushed by local Taurs?! Sad, but so delicious."};
descriptions["9754"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["9755"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["9757"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["9758"]={cn:"传说中的铁胃公会发明了这种可口的食物。他们使用自制的辣酱来提升公会会员的消化能力。",en:"This delicious recipe was invented by the Guild of the Iron Stomach, who used their own spicy ingredients to develop their members\' digestive capacities."};
descriptions["9759"]={cn:"一块美味的旋鸟肉，几个可口的蘑菇。你还能要求什么？如果不太老就好了...",en:"A good whirloin steak, some appetizing mushrooms. What more could you ask for? Maybe a slightly less chewy texture..."};
descriptions["9760"]={cn:"功效良多。",en:"Ah dinnae ken, but ah reckon \'at might be a plate o\' pottid heid..."};
descriptions["9764"]={cn:"即便是波特也是要上厕所的。",en:"Yes, this really is what you think... Even Polters have needs, after all."};
descriptions["9765"]={cn:"由波特的爪子残留物制成。现在你明白为什么他们这么粘了...",en:"This glue is made from residue found on Polters\' paws. That also explains why they\'re so sticky..."};
descriptions["9766"]={cn:"并不是所有的波特都是死气沉沉、又哭又闹的。他们中的一部分十分享受死后的生活。",en:"Not all Polters are sulky and moody, you know. Some of them are rather enjoying the afterlife!"};
descriptions["9774"]={cn:"将住在宫殿里的人炸上天...",en:"To liven life in the palace up a bit..."};
descriptions["9775"]={cn:"你好，我的名字叫爆弹。詹姆斯·爆弹。",en:"Have you met our secret agent bomb? Now you have..."};
descriptions["9776"]={cn:"扎克走遍了全世界，在炸弹爆炸前把它们收起来。但是旅途劳顿，他最终还是累得把自己炸死了。",en:"Zak travelled all around the World, collecting bombs before they exploded. But the journeying got to be too much for him, and in the end he exploded himself."};
descriptions["9777"]={cn:"这个豆子想找麻烦。",en:"This bean is looking for trouble."};
descriptions["9778"]={cn:"别用来抽打太敏感的屁股！",en:"Not to be used on sensitive butts!"};
descriptions["9779"]={cn:"土匪头子用来系裤子的布，打劫的时候就用来做旗帜，真是太机灵了！",en:"A piece of the chef\'s loincloth that can also be used as a banner - How ingenious!"};
descriptions["9781"]={cn:"并不仅仅是一颗普通的珍珠。假货也有自己的价值。",en:"A Sham Pearl is not just a simple pearl. It\'s a pearl who understands the meaning of life, the ultimate goal of existence! In other words, being a pearl."};
descriptions["9782"]={cn:"据说是属于情人的石头。当然你也可以往情敌的脸上砸。",en:"The stone of lovers, as they say! But you could also use it to throw at anyone who gets a little too close to your sweetheart."};
descriptions["9783"]={cn:"稀有的宝石，很容易招来小偷。",en:"The problem with rubies is that, as well being rare, they are particularly conspicuous and can attract bandits like a magnet. You\'ll see!"};
descriptions["9785"]={cn:"让宝藏猎人来为你算算命...然后将你洗劫一空。",en:"This type of crystal allows an Enutrofette to tell your fortune... And rip you off."};
descriptions["9786"]={cn:"啊，终于有些可以入眼的东西了！",en:"Ah, finally something lalovely to lalook at!"};
descriptions["9787"]={cn:"骑士们曾坚信在这种宝石的核心中有一个微缩的宇宙。事实上，那只是夜晚天空的倒影...",en:"The Iops used to think that a tiny version of the constellations could be found in the center of this precious stone. It was actually just a reflection of the sky."};
descriptions["9788"]={cn:"熠熠生辉的宝石。没有人能质疑它的存在感。",en:"This stone is so well polished, it excuses itself for its very existence."};
descriptions["9789"]={cn:"这颗蓝宝石拥有着比普通的石头两倍以上的光芒，它的光芒既吸引着埃努卓人的目光，同时也可以成为让伊欧普笨蛋保持距离的武器。",en:"This sapphire is doubly useful. It\'s both a glittering jewel to seduce rich Enutrofs, or a sharp defensive weapon to keep insistent Iops away."};
descriptions["9790"]={cn:"你肯定想能留下这个漂亮的小东西...记得千万不要给宝藏猎人发现。",en:"Here\'s a nice little find you\'re going to want to keep to yourself... And certainly not show to any Enutrofs."};
descriptions["9791"]={cn:"据报道，这种粪便具有难以置信的和谐能力。用它来造你的房子，你就永无邻里矛盾啦！",en:"This dung reportedly has incredible powers of isolation. Build your house with it, and you won\'t have any trouble with the neighbors."};
descriptions["9792"]={cn:"作为传统，宝藏猎人在婚礼上会献给新娘一颗鲜花簇拥的珍珠。恩，这就是他们泡妞的方式。",en:"Enutrofs traditionally give young Enutrofettes pearls in flowers during their nuptials. That way, they get to keep the pearl and the girl."};
descriptions["9793"]={cn:"如果你的生活需要一点浪漫，你可以邀请仰慕的对象共进月亮石晚餐。",en:"If you want a little romance in your life, you could use this stone to convince the object of your affections to go for a Moonstonelit dinner with you."};
descriptions["9795"]={cn:"和宝藏猎人学徒期望的不同，这块石头并不能预知未来。它只是块漂亮的石头。",en:"Contrary to what Enutrof\'s disciples may think, you cannot tell the future from this stone. It\'s just very pretty."};
descriptions["9796"]={cn:"和名字完全相反，这块石头一点也不可爱。",en:"Contrary to what its name implies, this rough stone isn\'t very lovely."};
descriptions["9797"]={cn:"由一名矿工根据他的爱人阿加莎命名。糟糕的是，他拼写很烂。不要在意细节。",en:"This stone was named by a miner, after his sweetheart, Agatha. Unfortunately he wasn\'t very good at spelling, but it\'s the thought that counts."};
descriptions["9798"]={cn:"不要被它的色彩和多样的外表迷惑了。毕竟它只是一块抛光的石头。",en:"Don\'t be too impressed by its color and generous forms. It\'s just a polished stone, after all!"};
descriptions["9800"]={cn:"既漂亮又锋利，这块石头割碎了很多矿工的手。",en:"As beautiful as it is sharp, this stone has cut many a greedy miner\'s hand."};
descriptions["9801"]={cn:"款待敌人的好礼物，也用来款待不请自来的远房阿姨。",en:"Ideal for giving your enemies the welcome they deserve, this venom will also prove a valuable ally in the event of a surprise visit from your great-aunt."};
descriptions["9802"]={cn:"在羊腿烤熟之后，就闻不到扑鼻的骚气了。",en:"If it\'s any consolation, at least when you burn the meat it covers up the repulsive smell of Gobball."};
descriptions["9803"]={cn:"会嗅嗅哦！至少曾经会。",en:"It really smells! Or, at least, it used to."};
descriptions["9804"]={cn:"几乎...是万恶之源。",en:"The essence of all evil... or almost!"};
descriptions["9805"]={cn:"当心，别虐待这些豆子。否则它们会把你卷上天。",en:"Be careful not to abuse these beans, or they might wind you up in return."};
descriptions["9806"]={cn:"千万不要去闻瓶子里的东西。土匪的口臭可不是闹着玩的...",en:"Try not to breathe in the contents of this flask. Bandits aren\'t exactly known for good oral hygiene..."};
descriptions["9808"]={cn:"一旦精灵被释放出来，他们只会做一件事情：附身于最近的人或物品，直到消亡。",en:"Once these little fairies have been released, there\'s only one thing they want to do: cling on to the nearest person or item until they fade away."};
descriptions["9811"]={cn:"给好孩子糖果是一种传统...奶奶说这让他们茁壮成长。",en:"It\'s traditional to give children candy if they\'ve been good... Grandma says it makes them big and strong."};
descriptions["9812"]={cn:"由一层尘土外衣包裹，将提高使用者的悟性。",en:"Well-preserved by a sturdy layer of dust, this candy will give great wisdom to whoever can stomach it."};
descriptions["9813"]={cn:"咕咕的彩色羽毛彰显睿智。只有老者才能穿它。",en:"This breastplate gets all its wisdom from the old Googoo hairs used to make it. Everybody knows that you need to be old to be egoodite."};
descriptions["9814"]={cn:"咕咕的彩色羽毛彰显睿智。只有老者才能穿它。",en:"This breastplate gets all its wisdom from the old Googoo hairs used to make it. Everybody knows that you need to be old to be egoodite."};
descriptions["9815"]={cn:"咕咕的彩色羽毛彰显睿智。只有老者才能穿它。",en:"This breastplate gets all its wisdom from the old Googoo hairs used to make it. Everybody knows that you need to be old to be egoodite."};
descriptions["9816"]={cn:"咕咕的彩色羽毛彰显睿智。只有老者才能穿它。",en:"This breastplate gets all its wisdom from the old Googoo hairs used to make it. Everybody knows that you need to be old to be egoodite."};
descriptions["9817"]={cn:"咕咕护符并不是一个太糟的选择...起码比没有好。",en:"A Googoo amulet isn\'t the worst thing you could have around your neck... It\'s not far off, though."};
descriptions["9818"]={cn:"咕咕护符并不是一个太糟的选择...起码比没有好。",en:"A Googoo amulet isn\'t the worst thing you could have around your neck... It\'s not far off, though."};
