descriptions["9867"]={cn:"给好孩子糖果是一种传统...奶奶说这让他们茁壮成长。",en:"It\'s traditional to give children candy if they\'ve been good... Grandma says it makes them big and strong."};
descriptions["9874"]={cn:"用于掩盖油光光的头发，也可用作纸巾。\n狂战士专用。",en:"This bandana is great for camouflaging a greasy mane of hair, and it can also be used as a tissue.\nSacriers only."};
descriptions["9875"]={cn:"用于掩盖油光光的头发，也可用作纸巾。\n狂战士专用。",en:"This bandana is great for camouflaging a greasy mane of hair, and it can also be used as a tissue.\nSacriers only."};
descriptions["9876"]={cn:"用于掩盖油光光的头发，也可用作纸巾。\n狂战士专用。",en:"This bandana is great for camouflaging a greasy mane of hair, and it can also be used as a tissue.\nSacriers only."};
descriptions["9877"]={cn:"用于掩盖油光光的头发，也可用作纸巾。\n狂战士专用。",en:"This bandana is great for camouflaging a greasy mane of hair, and it can also be used as a tissue.\nSacriers only."};
descriptions["9879"]={cn:"据说防狼作用出众，这就是为什么治愈者喜欢它的原因。当她们要去深山老林里探访隐士的时候特别有用。",en:"It\'s said that this headgear keeps Boowolves away, which is probably why Eniripsas like it so much, especially when they have to visit invalids who live deep in the forest."};
descriptions["9891"]={cn:"极轻的匕首。虽然不太锋利，但是可以很迅速地攻击敌人。",en:"This exceptionally light dagger might not be very sharp, but you can hit very quickly with it."};
descriptions["9927"]={cn:"现在没人敢说你穷得没内裤穿了！",en:"No one will be able to say you\'re not wearing any underwear now!"};
descriptions["9930"]={cn:"平淡无奇的木板，吸收攻击。",en:"This shield really can chew all that it bites off."};
descriptions["9932"]={cn:"献给单刷狂热者！",en:"For diehard singletons!"};
descriptions["9933"]={cn:"穿过迷雾，看清未来。至少可以预知临近的失败。",en:"This ring can see into the mists of your future, at least as far as the horrific defeat that\'s just around the corner."};
descriptions["9934"]={cn:"手上带着如此诱人的戒指，当心别一口咬下去了。",en:"With such an appetizing ring on your finger, you\'ll need to be careful you don\'t bite it clean off. Dough!"};
descriptions["9935"]={cn:"欧拉，一名金匠，某天晚上在地窖里发现了一枚漂亮的结婚戒指。她给戒指镶嵌了一枚钻石，拿到阿玛克纳拍卖场买了出去。",en:"Ora the Eniripsette, a goldsmith by trade, found this pretty wedding ring by chance in a tavern one night. She decided to set a jewel in it and sell it at the Amakna auction."};
descriptions["9936"]={cn:"一个精巧便携的实验小瓶，在需要的时候用得上。",en:"This ring holds a tiny, portable flask which will make you more resistant in times of need."};
descriptions["9940"]={cn:"用于展示优质商品！\n放在庇护袋的交易屋里。",en:"Useful for showing off your best products!\nPut it in the Trade Room in your Haven Bag."};
descriptions["9942"]={cn:"并不太锋利，但是依然能给人以疼痛。",en:"This blade may not be sharp, but it certainly smarts!"};
descriptions["9948"]={cn:"如果敌人不肯从你的视线里撤退，那么它可以帮你剪断敌人的魔爪。",en:"If an enemy won\'t get his paws out of your business, then this shovel should help you cut him down to size."};
descriptions["9950"]={cn:"点击两下来把整组古代资源转换成新的资源。古代资源需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["9951"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["9952"]={cn:"布拉克玛的家常饰物，象征着对于力量的崇拜。把它磨成粉末的话，也可以做成苦味粗薄饼。",en:"The Scara Horn is a symbol of veneration in many Brakmarian households. If you grind it down to powder you can also use it to make very bitter and gritty pancakes."};
descriptions["9953"]={cn:"独角仙死亡的时候，心脏也会迅速腐蚀。收集它们的心脏很难，所以格外珍贵。",en:"Generally speaking, Scara Hearts decompose instantly when they die, which makes collecting them a particularly difficult job."};
descriptions["9954"]={cn:"从前，狼毛被用来制作宗教粉刷。热爱动物的治愈者们牺牲性命，终于阻止了这一愚行。",en:"Once upon a time, Boowolf hairs were used to make ritual paintbrushes. The high death rate of Eniripsas trying to obtain them soon put an end to this practice."};
descriptions["9955"]={cn:"相传查理·爱德森曾经吃过这种肉排，但是实际上它的肉实在太坚硬了，以至于你想要烹调它必须使用火焰喷射器。",en:"Charlie Endstown-Smisse was rumored to eat nothing but raw Boowolf steak. That\'s not much of an achievement: this meat is so tough it never cooks, even if you blast it with a flame thrower."};
descriptions["9956"]={cn:"这些烧瓶中的东西很容易制作，它有点新鲜藏红花的味道，只要一滴就会让喝进它的人痛苦不堪。",en:"These flasks, which can be easily reproduced, smell of fresh saffron and instill strength and suffering in anyone who drinks them."};
descriptions["9957"]={cn:"甲虫壳的的作用大多数用来制作盾牌，盔甲，斧以及摇篮。",en:"Scarapaces are mostly used to make shields, armor, axes, and cradles."};
descriptions["9958"]={cn:"在倒霉的一天之后，没有什么能比一杯冰凉的啤酒更提神的了。",en:"Nothing like a nice cool root beer on a sunny afternoon to forget your latest heartbreak!"};
descriptions["9959"]={cn:"收录于著名的《旅行者传送指南》丛书中。",en:"This is from the famous \"Zaapackers guide...\" collection."};
descriptions["9962"]={cn:"宠物装备可以于宠物设定介面中更改。此物品已无用处，可以将其分解掉。",en:"Pet equipment can be changed in the pet settings interface. This item is obsolete; you can recycle it."};
descriptions["9963"]={cn:"对于双手简直是灾难，太重了。送一套给敌人吧，压死他们。",en:"These cards are disasters on legs. Send a few into enemy ranks to wreak havoc!"};
descriptions["9964"]={cn:"虽然看起来很好吃的样子，但是如果一口咬上去会影响战斗效果。",en:"This juicy bow may look absolutely delicious, but gnawing on it will only make it less effective on the battlefield."};
descriptions["9965"]={cn:"出乎意料，这根指针并没有死去。它习惯杀戮。",en:"Despite what you might think, this clock hand isn\'t actually dead. It just likes killing others."};
descriptions["9966"]={cn:"为频繁放弃战斗的人特意准备，并不会让你变得更勇敢，只是让你更善于逃命！",en:"All those who continually flee fights, this is the wand for you. It won\'t actually make you any braver, but it will make you better at running away!"};
descriptions["9967"]={cn:"阴险的利刃，时刻寻找着背后补刀的机会。",en:"These sneaky blades always find just the right moment to attack from behind."};
descriptions["9968"]={cn:"判断一个人是不是个江湖阿飞，并不仅仅是看此人的财富，更要看他的生活态度。带上这柄剑，你看起来英俊潇洒，即便你身无分文。",en:"You can tell a Hohoglian by his wealth, of course, but also by his haughty attitude. Carry this blade and you\'ll look elegant and well-to-do, even if you don\'t have a kama to your name."};
descriptions["9969"]={cn:"由伟大的卡尔·格劳乔制造，他是痞子联盟的守护者。他在他的墓碑上刻上了他的名言“经验使人上瘾”。",en:"This sword was made by the great Karl Groucho, defender of the Hoglians. He engraved his famous maxim in its side: \"XP is the opium of the people.\""};
descriptions["9970"]={cn:"由一个疯狂的产品经理发明。他被邻居房子里发出的吵闹低音逼疯了。他用自己的发明把邻居的烦人音响砸了个稀巴烂。",en:"This weapon was invented by a smith who was sick of the booming bass coming from his neighbors\' house. He used his creation to smash the source of their anti-social behavior to smithereens."};
descriptions["9971"]={cn:"一丝一毫的裂缝都不放过。",en:"A cheeky staff."};
descriptions["9972"]={cn:"你大可以吹嘘说这把斧头可以裂天碎地。吹，接着吹。",en:"You can claim that this can slice the sky, but you\'ll just be blowing hot air."};
descriptions["9973"]={cn:"如果你对于腐尸的气味毫不在意，那么这根棍子肯定能满足你的各种变态需求。",en:"If you can get over the deathly stench, this club is sure to satisfy your more morbid urges."};
descriptions["9974"]={cn:"迪娜·米蒂制造的锤子，用来打碎敌人虚伪的笑容。",en:"A hammer created by Ms. Dinah Mitee, who used it to smash her enemies\' smiles off their faces."};
descriptions["9975"]={cn:"死灵护盾...长大了之后想做个喇叭！",en:"The Necrofahrt shield - it wanted to be a trumpet when it was growing up!"};
descriptions["9976"]={cn:"死也不认错。",en:"This shield is frequently wrong, but it will never admit it."};
descriptions["9977"]={cn:"阴险的利刃，时刻寻找着背后补刀的机会。",en:"These sneaky blades always find just the right moment to attack from behind."};
descriptions["9978"]={cn:"阴险的利刃，时刻寻找着背后补刀的机会。",en:"These sneaky blades always find just the right moment to attack from behind."};
descriptions["9979"]={cn:"阴险的利刃，时刻寻找着背后补刀的机会。",en:"These sneaky blades always find just the right moment to attack from behind."};
descriptions["9980"]={cn:"漂亮的肩甲，和红辣椒完美搭配。如果你能找到任何一个，那简直是...",en:"These pretty epaulettes would go quite well with chili. If you can find any, that is..."};
descriptions["9981"]={cn:"不要想着说服这件胸甲。它始终是正确的！",en:"Don\'t even bother arguing with this breastplate. It\'s ALWAYS right!"};
descriptions["9983"]={cn:"立正！放规矩点！让我们看看称职的警卫的样子！",en:"Stand up straight and show some discipline! Show us a guard who\'s worthy of his title!"};
descriptions["9984"]={cn:"恶心反胃？妈妈说快用布丁啉。",en:"Upset stomach? Clever moms use Evervom!"};
descriptions["9989"]={cn:"绿成这样的斗篷一定会给你带来好运的！",en:"A cape as green as this will certainly bring you luck!"};
descriptions["9993"]={cn:"现在人们想偷看你们会很难，无论是从正面还是背面。",en:"Now people will have trouble sneaking up on you, from behind or from in front."};
descriptions["9994"]={cn:"看起来你有点过时了！",en:"Looks like you\'ve gone a bit overboard!"};
descriptions["10005"]={cn:"你发现这件护符很烦人，因为上面的触须不停地挠你的胸脯。",en:"Wearers usually find this necklace really irritating, thanks to its decorative moustaches which tend to tickle the chest."};
descriptions["10006"]={cn:"你发现这件护符很烦人，因为上面的触须不停地挠你的胸脯。",en:"Wearers usually find this necklace really irritating, thanks to its decorative moustaches which tend to tickle the chest."};
descriptions["10007"]={cn:"你发现这件护符很烦人，因为上面的触须不停地挠你的胸脯。",en:"Wearers usually find this necklace really irritating, thanks to its decorative moustaches which tend to tickle the chest."};
descriptions["10008"]={cn:"这个树枝不会教你人生经验，但它会让你种出一棵雄壮的倒栽树。",en:"This cutting won\'t teach you about life, but it will allow you to grow a magnificent Boabob."};
descriptions["10009"]={cn:"看见这棵倒栽树没？虽然摸起来很柔顺，但和伊欧普一样壮。",en:"Can you see this Boabob? It\'s smooth to the touch, but as strong as a Iop!"};
descriptions["10010"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["10012"]={cn:"能让你比以往更加光彩夺目，虽然你最终还是没收到什么派对邀请。",en:"You still might not get invited to many garden parties, but this bow does make you look a bit more impressive than before."};
descriptions["10015"]={cn:"简易的法杖，打人也不太痛。人们用它来敲打龙鸟的头，以保证不走错路。",en:"This basic supple staff doesn\'t hurt very much: inoffensive, it was specially invented for hitting Dragoturkeys in the middle of the head to guide them."};
descriptions["10020"]={cn:"一旦你触摸到这柄被诅咒的宝剑，你就再也无法摆脱它了。你只有哀叹的份...",en:"Now you\'ve got your hands on this haunted sword, you\'ll never be able to get rid of it. All you can do is wail miserably about your fate..."};
descriptions["10022"]={cn:"使尽全力扔出这把锤子，会划出一条十分奇怪的轨迹。锤子在空中转了无数圈，最后仍然命中目标。",en:"When you throw this hammer with all your might, it takes a pretty strange trajectory. It spirals around violently, but still manages to hit its target."};
descriptions["10023"]={cn:"传说大沃特将锤子交给了一个路过的可怜小布丁。她觉得这样做的话，所有的烦恼都能迎刃而解。对你有用吗？",en:"Legend says that Great Water offered this hammer to a sad, little Puddly passing by. She seemed pretty convinced that all her problems would come out in the wash. Will it work for you?"};
descriptions["10024"]={cn:"如果不能按照椭圆轨迹挥舞这把铲子，你自己就会不停地转一整天圈！",en:"If you don\'t shake this spade in an elliptical manner, you\'ll be going round in circles all day!"};
descriptions["10027"]={cn:"举高点！它能保护你牙齿不被打掉。",en:"Hold it high, it might just keep your teeth from being knocked out."};
descriptions["10029"]={cn:"静下心来仔细聆听，可以听到从远古时期传来的歌声，回忆起无畏的少年。",en:"If you listen carefully, you can hear this ring humming old tunes from the Dofus Era, like those of Jon Lemon."};
descriptions["10030"]={cn:"在诺维亚冰河之心炼成，那里充斥着巨魔和各种传奇。诺维亚人实在太少了！",en:"This ring was forged at the heart of the Norveijian glaciers, in lands marked by Trools and legends. Those Norveijians are absolutely precious!"};
descriptions["10031"]={cn:"指环内壁上铭刻着新手入门教程。你知道的，万一真的有菜鸟不知道戒指戴哪里...",en:"Apparently the craftsman who made this ring thought it was important to inscribe instructions for use along the inside. You know, in case the wearer had forgotten where his fingers were..."};
descriptions["10032"]={cn:"老宾逊的戒指！这下你明白了为什么有股鱼腥味...",en:"This is Gropinson Cruizzo\'s ring! That explains the fishy smell..."};
descriptions["10033"]={cn:"刺鼻的气味不仅赶走了你的敌人，也吓跑了队友。显然和平是需要代价的。",en:"The strong odor emanating from this ring can send your enemies running for the hills... and your allies, too. They do say peace comes at a price."};
descriptions["10034"]={cn:"小心。它对敌我两方都很危险。",en:"Watch out for this ring. It can be as dangerous for you as for your enemies."};
descriptions["10035"]={cn:"带来好运？一点也不。只是看起来很漂亮。",en:"Is it lucky? Neigh, but it looks lovely!"};
descriptions["10036"]={cn:"常年浸泡于海水中。就算不小心掉到海里，也没什么大不了。",en:"This amulet has been soaked in sea water since it was very young. If you drop it in a lake, it\'s not the end of the World."};
descriptions["10037"]={cn:"倔强得像头驴，精通自我保护之道。",en:"An amulet that is a stubborn as a donkey, but knows how to watch its back!"};
descriptions["10038"]={cn:"如果你找不到恋人眼中的光芒，那就试试这个项链。",en:"You can\'t see the stars in your sweetheart\'s eyes... But at least you can always find them in this amulet."};
descriptions["10040"]={cn:"有点紧，瘦身佳品。",en:"This amulet is certainly a tight fit: it\'s great if you\'re seriously looking to lose some weight."};
descriptions["10041"]={cn:"那个可怕的治愈者库伊莉莎恶魔曾经从把剥掉了一百零一张她敌人的皮来做这双鞋，但是这双鞋穿起来实在是太太太舒服了！",en:"That horrible Eniripsa Cruelisa DeMon apparently skinned 101 enemies to make these boots, but they\'re sooo soft and comfortable!"};
descriptions["10042"]={cn:"下次再往木头上敲钉子的时候，记住把你的脚伸远点。不然你就得一瘸一拐地走路了。",en:"Next time you need to knock on wood, you\'ll only have to reach as far as your feet. Careful, they\'re uncomfy as anything and they\'ll stop you from walking straight."};
descriptions["10043"]={cn:"你得承认这些东西有那么一点艺术品位，但是细节太不到位了，所以很快穿坏了，然后被丢弃，被彻底忘记。就像你这个人一样，你被遗忘得更快。",en:"These sandals, which were made with little artistic flair and no attention to detail, quickly fell into disrepair and were forgotten. Like you, but they lasted a bit longer."};
descriptions["10044"]={cn:"酷毙了！",en:"Cooool, man!"};
descriptions["10045"]={cn:"这双皮靴带来很多好处：增强体质，让你从头到尾容光焕发。看起来是唤兽师的最佳选择。",en:"These boots are full of wonderful things that will improve your health and make your fur shine from your ears to the tip of your tail. It would seem they work best on Osamodas."};
descriptions["10046"]={cn:"穿上它，再也不用惧怕任何战斗了！",en:"With these Moogrrtrool Boots on, you\'ll really know how to kick your opponent into shape!"};
descriptions["10047"]={cn:"看上去普普通通，但是拥有强大魔力！会使主人对于任何不看路的家伙隐形。多么的不可思议！",en:"This cloak may look ordinary, but it has magical powers! It will make its wearer invisible to anyone who isn\'t looking their way. Impressive!"};
descriptions["10051"]={cn:"在吃了一碗热腾腾的卷心菜汤之后，这条腰带帮你抑制住想放屁的冲动。",en:"This belt will keep your gas under wraps after a steaming bowl of cabbage soup."};
descriptions["10052"]={cn:"按摩效果极佳。幸运的主人得以免受压力困扰，用更好的准备去面对挑战。",en:"This belt has a really nice massaging effect on its wearer\'s skin. The lucky owner ends up less stressed and is thus more ready to react in battle."};
descriptions["10053"]={cn:"如果你喜欢在沙滩上裸奔，你一定会爱上这个腰带，它至少可以适当地遮一下某个地方。",en:"If you love running naked along beaches, you\'re sure to love this belt, which doubles up as a fig-leaf replacement. There\'s even a place to keep some self-tanning lotion behind the buckle."};
descriptions["10054"]={cn:"懒散的生活方式必备。它会不断的自动松开。",en:"This belt, adapted to a depraved lifestyle, has a habit of undoing itself faster than its own shadow."};
descriptions["10058"]={cn:"用于存放你的厨具。",en:"These epaulettes are a useful place to keep your cooking utensils."};
descriptions["10060"]={cn:"这对护肩并不能让你光彩照人，但是款式新颖，依然能让你光鲜亮丽。",en:"These indiscrete epaulettes might not make you feel very illuminated, but they are so original you\'ll shine in society anyway."};
descriptions["10063"]={cn:"看起来很脆弱，一用才知道强大。",en:"This breastplate looks fragile, but once you know how to use it, it\'s incredibly powerful!"};
descriptions["10069"]={cn:"点击两下来把整组古代资源转换成新的资源。古代资源需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["10070"]={cn:"你可以通过扭曲的外表以及惊人的硬度辨别出鸵鸟嘴。许多布拉克玛的小孩在换牙齿的时候咬鸵鸟嘴来镇静自己。",en:"You can recognize Strich Beaks by their twisted appearance and their astonishing resistance. Many Brakmarian babies were given these to use as pacifiers when their teeth were coming through."};
descriptions["10071"]={cn:"在路上遇到一枚完好无损的巨蛋是不太常见的事情，你要是看见里面有小鸟正在往外啄可不要大惊小怪。",en:"Owning a Gigantegg in perfect condition is as rare as it is cumbersome. Don\'t be surprised if you feel little bird pecks coming from inside it."};
descriptions["10073"]={cn:"重辣调味，经过数天卤制之后，再煮个半天，终于可以吃了。",en:"Prepared with strong spices, marinated a few days in an overpowering sauce, and cooked for a great many hours, this Strich Neck can just about pass for edible."};
descriptions["10074"]={cn:"可以制成羽毛笔，也可以插在帽子上。",en:"Some wonderful books have been written with quills made from Strich Feathers. You can also use it to decorate your hat."};
descriptions["10076"]={cn:"完美展现了西尔维斯特的糟糕性格：一个远近闻名的挑剔客户，态度粗暴。唯一使他感兴趣的东西是他的娃娃...",en:"This ring represents Sylvester\'s bitterness perfectly: known for being a really spiny customer, with a manner as coarse and dry as kindlewood, the only thing he has any time for is his dolls..."};
descriptions["10077"]={cn:"查姆是个阴谋大师。他善于用计谋瓦解敌人，然后把他们当成傀儡一样玩耍，无论敌人是生是死。",en:"Charm excels in the art of manipulation and is feared for his ability to tear apart any enemy and make them dance to his tune, dead or alive."};
descriptions["10078"]={cn:"西尔维斯特战斗时总是挥舞法杖，吓唬敌人。他喜欢看到敌人四处奔逃，夹着尾巴发抖的样子。",en:"Sylvester likes to start a fight by waving his staff around to intimidate his victims. He loves seeing them run away, trembling like leaves and with their tails between their legs."};
descriptions["10080"]={cn:"时髦的头盔，让你像发情的绵绵一样高兴得跳起来。对于心脏不好的人无用...",en:"This exhilarating helmet will make you jump for joy like a Gobbette in heat. Not for the faint-hearted..."};
descriptions["10081"]={cn:"用于保护萨迪达少女免受大坏狼骚扰。但是，为什么颤抖的树叶会有一条...",en:"This amulet was made to protect Sadidettes terrified of running into a big bad Boowolf. Why the Trembling Leaf had one, on the other hand, is a mystery..."};
descriptions["10082"]={cn:"阿莱利亚对她的娃娃痴迷到了极点...她用剩下的材料制造了一个超常的戒指。",en:"Aralia loved her dolls... to the point of obsession. She used some of their remains to make this unconventional ring."};
descriptions["10083"]={cn:"阿莱利亚·斯皮诺莎最喜欢的戒指，这个漂亮的蓝戒指（有点脏）可以轻易地将敌人引诱到泥潭里。",en:"Aralia Spinosa\'s favorite jewel, this magnificent blue ring (which is a bit on the grotty side) will allow you to lead your enemies into the mud with ease."};
descriptions["10084"]={cn:"点击两下来把整组古代资源转换成新的资源。古代资源需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["10086"]={cn:"有人说哪怕是一只鸵鸟上的两条腿，要完全相像也是不可能的。",en:"Some claim it\'s impossible to find two Strich legs of exactly the same size, even if you take them from the same bird."};
descriptions["10087"]={cn:"小老鼠们都应该在衣橱里备上一些，万一不小心撞到喵喵，穿着这个会显得优雅一点。",en:"All little rats should have one of these in their wardrobe. It turns elegantly when you dance too close to a Bow Meow."};
descriptions["10088"]={cn:"说这双皮靴能奔跑如飞的人可不是在开玩笑：如果你抓住了它们，请确保鞋带已经系牢！",en:"Whoever told you these boots run really fast wasn\'t joking: if you ever manage to catch them, make sure you strap them tightly to your feet!"};
descriptions["10089"]={cn:"除了做饭以外，什么都会。",en:"These Estrichettes do everything except the cooking."};
descriptions["10090"]={cn:"贝特隆克十分喜爱这件胸甲。对他来说，生命一晃而过。",en:"Bertronche loved his strichplate. He liked watching life slip by."};
descriptions["10091"]={cn:"吹啊吹，让这风儿吹，吹得斗笠到处飞。",en:"The wind is constantly filling up this hat and lifting it straight off your head."};
descriptions["10092"]={cn:"比想象中的更黑，好像能吞没整个宇宙，却又如此的迷人，让你忘乎所以。",en:"This ring is much heavier than you\'d expect and it looks like it could swallow the whole universe. But it\'s so pretty you\'d forgive it anything."};
descriptions["10093"]={cn:"巨魔们真心喜欢新鲜的鸵鸟脖子配蛋黄酱，装在这样的盘子里端上来。他们如果点这个的话，别犹豫就照这么做。",en:"Trools absolutely adore freshly sliced strich necks dipped in the yolk of this shield. If they ask you for it, hand it over without a murmur."};
descriptions["10094"]={cn:"鸵鸟袋？或者是关于鸵鸟的袋子？\n这是个好问题...",en:"Strich Bag? Or Bag of Strich?\nThat is the question..."};
descriptions["10095"]={cn:"这把手杖曾经属于一个疯子。你能用它读懂鸵鸟的想法。还算不赖，对吧。",en:"This wand once belonged to Jonah Dward. You can use it to read a strich\'s thoughts. That\'s not so bad, you say."};
descriptions["10096"]={cn:"太阳下山后，腰带上的狼毛愈发的柔软贴身。",en:"The hairs on this very soft belt become strangely clingy when the sun goes down."};
descriptions["10097"]={cn:"狼会因为各种小虫子搅扰无法入眠。多亏了这顶帽子，现在你也有了同样的权利。",en:"Boowolves fall pray to countless little nocturnal parasites. Thanks to this hat, you too can benefit from the extra waking hours they add to your day."};
descriptions["10098"]={cn:"没有比肩膀上戴着两个狼爪更可靠的了。然而你有没有觉得在夜晚，狼爪好像总会变长一点...？",en:"What could be more reassuring than having two enormous Boowolf paws on your shoulders? Though have you noticed how the claws always feel like they\'re getting longer at night...?"};
descriptions["10099"]={cn:"重量和一头死去的哞哞差不多，能防水防狼。有时候，巨魔们甚至将它用作镜子。",en:"The Foolmoun weighs about as much as a dead Moogrr, but it\'s waterproof and resistant to Boowolf scratches. Sometimes, Trools even use it as a mirror."};
descriptions["10100"]={cn:"狼毛加厚，防风防雨。虽然不如神秘的满月护盾结实，抵挡小家伙们的攻击还是绰绰有余。",en:"This shield has been weatherproofed using Boowolf hairs. It\'s not as efficient as the mythical Foolmoun, but it provides pretty good protection against droplets."};
descriptions["10101"]={cn:"狼祭司用配偶的颅骨制成了这柄法杖。魔力并不强，但我保证你会记住管家婆的力量。",en:"Boowolfines make these staffs from the skulls of their former spouses. They might not be very magical, but they will make sure you never forget who wears the pants."};
descriptions["10102"]={cn:"仿佛踩着敌人的尸体前进。晚上，它们会发出令人胆寒的声音。",en:"These boots give you the strange sensation of walking on your opponents\' remains. At night, especially, they make some very unnerving sounds."};
descriptions["10105"]={cn:"得到这顶旋鸟头盔之后，有人往头盔上缝上了紫色的丝线，希望让它更漂亮些。众口难调，不是所有人都喜欢同一种风格。但是起码它让你在人群里异常显眼。",en:"Upon finding this Whirligig Helmet, someone sewed purple thread into it to make it prettier. It\'s not to everyone\'s taste, but at least you\'ll stand out from the crowd."};
descriptions["10106"]={cn:"毫无疑问，是你见过的最性感的胖次！舒适贴身，优雅紧致！",en:"These are definitely the nicest panties you\'ll ever see! They\'re so light and comfortable that your movements will become more graceful when you wear them."};
descriptions["10107"]={cn:"威尔是个弱小愚笨的孩子，他喜欢赌博。这个崭新的戒指由稀有金属制成，有力地证明了这一点。",en:"Will was neither strong nor intelligent, but he did love gambling. This brand new ring, made from rare metals, is incontestable proof of that."};
descriptions["10108"]={cn:"威尔·雅穆特尔始终脾气火爆。他对于箭术毫无兴趣。事实上，在脾气暴躁的假面具下，他只是个可怜的懦夫。",en:"Will Yamtell was known for his ability to get things off to an explosive start. Far from being passionate about archery, though, he was just a pathetic coward who hid behind his fiery temper."};
descriptions["10109"]={cn:"夏勒亲自制造了这只护符。它的指针旋转速度飞快，完全吸引了敌人的注意力。",en:"Xaler made this amulet himself. Its hand turns at a very unnatural speed, completely distracting all his enemies."};
descriptions["10110"]={cn:"极受欢迎的腰带，无论是谁穿上它都能进入催眠状态...",en:"This belt is highly sought-after because whoever equips it enters into a trance in which they see the galloooping haaands of tiiime slooowing dooown ooon the liiit diiiaaaaals."};
descriptions["10111"]={cn:"象征着胡尔夫用指针九头蛇施放的火焰。随着岁月流逝，他慢慢放下了不可触及的爱情。",en:"This ring symbolizes the flame Xulf bestowed upon his Hydrand. It represents his heart, which withered over time as he came to understand impossibility of their love."};
descriptions["10112"]={cn:"由抗腐蚀金属制成。稀有品质经得起时间考验，这也是为什么时间法师对这个挂坠如此感兴趣的原因。",en:"This amulet is made from corrosion-resistant metals. This rare quality makes it a timeless jewel, which is probably why Xelors are so interested in it."};
descriptions["10113"]={cn:"这个美丽的指环是整个套装中心脏一般的存在...它还在跳动！",en:"This beautiful ring is set with a little Scarafly heart. It\'s still warm."};
descriptions["10114"]={cn:"这个指环上镶嵌着金甲虫卵，当你佩戴它的时候请你保证其安全和适当的温度，天知道它会孵化出什么来。",en:"This ring is set with a little golden Scara egg. Keep it safe and warm while you\'re wearing it. You never know what genius might hatch."};
descriptions["10115"]={cn:"有了这条腰带，所有的女孩都会想要乘坐你的龙鸟快线，你会因此而出名甚至是被爱。",en:"With this belt, all the girls will want to drive your Dragoturkey. You will be famous, and maybe even in love."};
descriptions["10116"]={cn:"你也会觉得这件披风给了你一对翅膀，但是只有笨蛋伊欧普人才会穿着它从悬崖上跳下来。",en:"You might feel like this cloak gives you wings, but only a Iop would be foolish enough to try jumping off a cliff while wearing it."};
descriptions["10117"]={cn:"这个看起来东方式的头盔时时刻刻提醒着你需要爱来呵护。",en:"This oriental looking hat is a constant reminder that all you need is love."};
descriptions["10118"]={cn:"财富使你如此耀眼。更准确地说，金色的油漆让你成为万众的焦点。",en:"You will shine with wealth. Or rather, \nyou will shine with gold paint topped with non-chip transparent nail polish."};
descriptions["10119"]={cn:"你可以时不时地闻闻，提醒你自己过往的欢乐时光。你也可以用它做一锅香气喷喷的汤。",en:"This is the sort of souvenir that you like to smell from time to time to remind you of the happy time you spent together. You can also turn it into a delicious sweet soup."};
descriptions["10120"]={cn:"绿色的，是绿色的染料！",en:"It\'s green, dabba dee dabba dye!"};
descriptions["10121"]={cn:"在没人的地方偷偷唱歌。",en:"This stone sings when nobody\'s around."};
descriptions["10123"]={cn:"仙女草种类繁多，各地不同。但是始终会带有一根贝拉的秀发以及亚麻花茎。",en:"The composition of these mixed herbs tends to vary from region to region, but they always contain a Bellaphone hair and a flax flower stem."};
descriptions["10124"]={cn:"一种美味的酱汁，美食家的最爱。食用后秀发笔直闪亮，肤色白净。有个小小的副作用：可能会放屁。",en:"Belchmel is a delicious, creamy sauce adored by foodies everywhere. It\'s said to make your hair straighter and shinier, and your complexion paler. The explosive burps it causes are a small price to pay."};
descriptions["10125"]={cn:"戴上之后，立刻成为舞会焦点。或者，你也可以去玩跳房子。",en:"When worn, this ring can make you the belle of the ball. Or, if you prefer a more gentle game, you can use it to play hopscotch."};
descriptions["10126"]={cn:"女骑士的最爱，男性穿上之后显得健壮有力。",en:"Iopettes love this helmet. It makes all the men who wear it look big and muscly."};
descriptions["10127"]={cn:"在地震的时候，能保证你双脚平稳。有人甚至声称它能控制造成地震的巨人们。",en:"This belt keeps you keep your feet on the ground during an earthquake. Some even say it controls the giants that cause them."};
descriptions["10128"]={cn:"看到披风上面又长又绿的纹饰了么，是变异虫流着口水爬过的痕迹。很粘人，不过很开胃。",en:"The long greenish lines on this cape are crawling with tiny slobbery larvas. They\'re a bit sticky, but very appetizing."};
descriptions["10130"]={cn:"你注定不会拥有它太久。它吸引着周围小偷的眼光，使他们想尽一切办法来偷走这枚戒指。但是总有一天还是会被别人再次偷走。好好珍惜...",en:"This ring won\'t be yours for very long. It brings out the green-eyed monster in others, who will want to steal it from you so that they, one day, can also have it snatched from them. Enjoy it while you can..."};
descriptions["10131"]={cn:"让你身心坚强，足以抵御敌人最猛烈的攻击。当然，如果你被巨人踩到了，别指望它能救你。",en:"This necklace will invigorate your body and spirit in order to resist the most bloody enemy assaults. Unfortunately, it won\'t save you from being crushed by a giant, rolling boulder."};
descriptions["10132"]={cn:"阿尔用这个金色戒指来闪瞎敌人的眼睛，迫使他们犯错。你得保证你自己的眼睛不被闪瞎...",en:"Al used this golden ring to reflect light towards his enemies, causing them to make mistakes. You can start by making sure you don\'t blind yourself with it..."};
descriptions["10133"]={cn:"戴的时间越长，贡献的意愿越强。",en:"This amulet will reduce your integrity to nothing: the more you wear it, the more devoted you will become to any cause whatsoever..."};
descriptions["10134"]={cn:"阿尔曾经被一只野鸭袭击过。从那以后，因为怕被打到脸，他制作了这只哨子。一旦有怪物接近，就吹哨子用刺耳的声音吓跑它们。",en:"Al was once attacked by a wild Kwak. Fearing disfigurement, he made this whistle, which will scare away any sort of monster with its ear-splitting notes."};
descriptions["10135"]={cn:"狂妄者械尼尔，梦想成为世界上最强的时间法师。人们不停地取笑他，所以他制造了这条腰带来，好让人们不敢小看他。",en:"Xunil the Megalomaniac wanted to become the best Xelor in the World. People made fun of him so much that he ended up making this \"Master of Time Belt\" so people would take him more seriously."};
descriptions["10136"]={cn:"如果你梦想远行，这个戒指是最佳伴侣。",en:"If you dream of visiting far off lands, Siksak the Transporter\'s ring is just what you need to go places."};
descriptions["10137"]={cn:"每次你施法的时候，腰带就开始吟唱不知名的旋律。不知道你的队友会不会喜欢...",en:"The holes in this belt are shaped to \"sing\" (off-key) a little song whenever you cast a spell. Not sure whether your team-mates will appreciate it..."};
descriptions["10138"]={cn:"通常只在黑市上出售的法杖，热衷于为你做各种脏活累活。任何阻拦它前进的东西都会被粉碎成渣。",en:"This staff, usually only sold on the black market, loves to do your dirty work for you. The faithful weapon will smash any skulls that get in its way to a pulp."};
descriptions["10139"]={cn:"据说能带来胜利的萨迪达护符。考虑到击败黑魔法的巨大代价，我才不会相信它...",en:"This Sadida amulet is supposed to guarantee victory in every battle. Given the beating the Black Birch took, I wouldn\'t really count on it..."};
descriptions["10140"]={cn:"像斯考奇一样，这枚戒指让人讨厌至极：一旦戴上，就永远取不下来了！它会像牛蝇叮粪便一样粘着你。",en:"Just like Skorch, this ring is a pain in the butt: once you\'ve touched it, you won\'t be able to get rid of it! It\'ll stick to you like a Moofly to a pile of dung."};
descriptions["10141"]={cn:"能轻易挑逗一群精力旺盛的年轻人打起来。这时候你需要一个治愈者...",en:"This belt can really put some oomph into a fight. Keep an Eniripsa close at hand!"};
descriptions["10142"]={cn:"里喀留斯从亚马逊女王，希波·丽塔那里偷来了这条腰带。能提高你的箭术。",en:"Lerakles stole this belt from the Anazome Queen, Hippo Lite. It\'ll improve some of your archery skills."};
descriptions["10143"]={cn:"易溶于水，所以你要保证在下雨的时候取下来！",en:"This attractive belt dissolves in water, so make sure you take it off when it rains!"};
descriptions["10144"]={cn:"完美的项链！温柔的暖意流入你的内心，鼓励你为悲伤的萨迪达少女英勇作战。同时也意味着刚正不阿。",en:"This amulet is perfect! Its gentle warmth will irradiate into your heart and make you a savior of Sadidette damsels in distress. \'Whiter-than-white\' smile included."};
descriptions["10145"]={cn:"金苹朵富含大量创生能量。海格力斯击败了花园守卫诺达尔，然后取走了很多金苹朵。",en:"After he\'d defeated Nodal, the garden guardian, Hairocles was able to steal as many of these apis, whose golden skin restores Wakfu, as he liked."};
descriptions["10146"]={cn:"选择这枚戒指需要做出一些牺牲。首当其冲的是你的手指，因为戒指实在太紧了，手指会变得跟风干香肠一样。",en:"If you wear this ring, you\'re going to have to be prepared to make a few sacrifices. The first is your finger itself, as the ring is so tight that it will turn into a hard little sausage."};
descriptions["10147"]={cn:"这个恼人的护符有一张大嘴，你最好让它闭着，否则够你受的。",en:"This annoying amulet may well have a mouth, but you\'re better off making sure it stays shut; if not, it might really give you an earful!"};
descriptions["10148"]={cn:"由超强力的催眠磁铁制成，看看它，肚子就饱了。",en:"This amulet, made from a particularly powerful and hypnotizing magnet, reduces the reflexes of anyone who stands gawping hungrily at it for too long."};
descriptions["10149"]={cn:"永远不要背对敌人：凶猛的腰带，即便敌人在你的背面，也能让你永远保持优势。",en:"You\'d better not turn your back on enemies: this vicious belt will prevent you from keeping the upper hand if someone happens to attack you from behind."};
descriptions["10150"]={cn:"罗宾喜欢人们看着她的眼睛。当她终于意识到自己并不起眼的时候，就用一只鸵鸟眼球制成了这条挂坠，挂在胸前。这下人们想不注意她都难。",en:"Robbyn liked it when people looked her in the eye.  Noticing that it didn\'t happen often, she made this amulet in the form of a Strich eye, and wore it strategically placed on her chest."};
descriptions["10151"]={cn:"看看罗宾吃了败仗之后的恼怒表情吧，趁你领先的时候放弃更好。",en:"Judging by the look on Robbyn\'s face when she loses a fight, it\'s probably a good idea to quit while you\'re ahead."};
descriptions["10152"]={cn:"怪不得头盔是绿油油的，原来是某位厨师用面粉和豆芙粪便烘焙出了这顶头盔。",en:"This helmet was cooked up by a chef out of flour and Tofu guano, which gives it its greenish tint. Then it was placed carefully in the oven..."};
descriptions["10153"]={cn:"能在昏暗的环境下发出些许光芒，十分有用，骑士制造。骑士居然也会做些有用的的事情了！",en:"This ring is capable of shedding light on bleak situations, making it very useful. Starting to see Iop inventors in a new light now, aren\'t you?"};
descriptions["10154"]={cn:"所有人都知道触摸到戒指的人会立刻变成超级斗士，不幸的是他的智商会归零。",en:"Everyone knows that whoever gets their hands on this ring immediately becomes a super tough fighter, unfortunately for whatever little bit of brain he has left."};
descriptions["10155"]={cn:"让所有戴的人缩水。如果你和牛头人一样强壮，你得小心不要缩水成啾啾的大小。",en:"This amulet shrinks whoever wears it. Wear it with moderation if you\'re as well-built as a Taur, or you\'ll end us as puny as a Piwi."};
descriptions["10156"]={cn:"几个蠢骑士制造了这条腰带，他们觉得为了潇洒吃点苦是应该的。你每走一步，腰带上的两根铁刺都会刺痛你的大腿。",en:"This belt, which was made by a group of Iops who preferred suffering to looking good, is armed with two big metal spikes which cut at your thighs with every step."};
descriptions["10157"]={cn:"你很少能遇见有想象力的骑士...因为觉得被孤立了，杜弗决定带上这条青绿色的腰带，在命运长路上找点乐子。",en:"You don\'t often come across an imaginative Iop... Feeling marginalized, Doof decided to wear this turquoise belt to poke fun at his destined path."};
descriptions["10158"]={cn:"和主人之间有着割不断的羁绊。它有着极强的占有欲，无论谁接近你，都会被它的嘲笑阻止。",en:"This amulet forms a very strong bond with its master. Loyal and possessive, if you didn\'t know better, you\'d swear it was hurling insults at anyone who gets too close to you."};
descriptions["10159"]={cn:"即便家里发生各种怪事，也没有人知道是这条腰带搞的鬼。今天也许你就会收到个惊喜！",en:"The general public don\'t know too much about the practices of belt fanatics, even if many of them do take place at home. You might be surprised!"};
descriptions["10160"]={cn:"语言沟通并不是肌肉男的强项。有个骑士花了整整一个秋天搞清楚怎么把这个戒指戴上。",en:"Communication isn\'t exactly Jo-Chlo Vandam\'s forte. It took a whole fall for the Iopette to figure out how to put this ring on."};
descriptions["10161"]={cn:"这戒指被诅咒了。据说造成了很多水手丧生，他们的船长在出海时就戴着它。",en:"This ring is jinxed. They say it led to the deaths of many sailors when their captain, remembering all the old wives\' tales, slipped it onto his finger when far out at sea."};
descriptions["10162"]={cn:"这份文件授予你\"968年最佳园林设计师\"称号。",en:"This document will enable you to prove your status as Landscaper of the Year 968."};
descriptions["10163"]={cn:"这份文件授予你\"967年最佳设计师\"称号。鲁邦·豹尾为你骄傲！",en:"This document will enable you to prove your status as Stylist of the Year 967. Lupene Jaguar-Tail would be proud!"};
descriptions["10164"]={cn:"阿斯皮顿总有办法找到他的戒指。无论是谁偷了他的戒指，他都会追踪到底...",en:"Aspidon has a gift which allows him to stay in contact with his ring. You can be sure he\'ll be able to track down whoever stole it from him..."};
descriptions["10165"]={cn:"阿斯皮顿平时总是围着女人转。在近身肉搏时，他用项链来锁住姑娘们的身体，也留住她们的心。",en:"A big fan of the ladies, Aspidon used his amulet to embrace lovely enemies and then break their hearts."};
descriptions["10178"]={cn:"有一件事是肯定的，斯奈弗才不在乎你的死活。不信？看看他给你的白眼吧。还是忘了这事吧...",en:"One thing\'s for sure, your health is not Snivel\'s concern, and if you need proof, just have a look at that black eye he gave you. Best forget about the whole thing..."};
descriptions["10179"]={cn:"开始是黄色，会随着你的心情变换颜色。它能让骑士和年轻的治愈者开心好久...",en:"This fun ring starts off yellow, but changes color to match your mood. It can keep Iops and young Eniripsas amused for hours..."};
descriptions["10180"]={cn:"餐后甜点之前，把这个戒指传来传去，帮助消化...",en:"The custom is to pass this ring from hand to hand just before dessert at banquets. Apparently, it eases digestion..."};
descriptions["10181"]={cn:"布鲁纳·菲尔古德从来就不是个斗士，从小就被父亲教育要体谅动物们的难处。当开始施展医术的时候，她可一点也不含糊。",en:"Bluna Feelgood was never much of a fighter, sensitized to monsters\' plight by her father\'s writings. When it came to healing, on the other hand, no one could hold a Cawwot to her."};
descriptions["10184"]={cn:"如果你暑假作业还没做完，这件肩甲将会给你一个睿智的忠告：管他咧。",en:"If you have bad posture, these epaulettes have some words of wisdom to share with you: Let it be."};
descriptions["10185"]={cn:"在护符上，你发现一行字：及时庆祝你的胜利吧，因为你不能到坟墓里去庆祝。械特罗夫。",en:"Engraved into this amulet, you\'ll find the words: \"Enjoy your victory while you can, because you won\'t be taking it to the grave. Xetrov.\""};
descriptions["10186"]={cn:"事实上，它的存在并不只会带来厄运，这个小指环也包含了一个很有趣的迷你翅膀，它会震动它的翅膀让你重新振作起来。",en:"Actually, it\'s not all that Sinister in the end. This little ring contains a funny mini-Sinistro who cheer you up any time by fluttering its little wings."};
descriptions["10187"]={cn:"稀有的腰带，价格昂贵。它的制造者在龙鸟快线打了很久临工才重新把它买回来。",en:"This rare and exceptional belt really did cost an arm and a leg. Its creator had to crawl inside a Dragoturkey to get it back."};
descriptions["10188"]={cn:"洛文的头实在太小了。所以无论她怎么戴，皇冠都会滑落到颈部。",en:"Ronwen\'s head was too small to wear this pretty diadem. So much so, in fact, that whenever she put it on, it would end up slipping down to her neck."};
descriptions["10189"]={cn:"举世闻名的哈里·罗特善于用他的情绪波动毒害治愈者的生命。",en:"The universally-despised Hairy Rotter is known for poisoning the lives of other Eniripsas with his terrible, and highly contagious, mood swings."};
descriptions["10190"]={cn:"得来不易的手环，见证了哈里·罗特以及他的朋友们的艰苦战斗历程。",en:"This bracelet, which had to be earned the hard way, has seen all manner of gruesome battles fought by Hairy Rotter and his admirable crew."};
descriptions["10191"]={cn:"哇吼！上面有一个小铃铛！",en:"Woohoo! It\'s got a little bell and everything!"};
descriptions["10192"]={cn:"如果你能毫不费力地系上这条腰带，它就会给你带来好运。",en:"This belt might bring you some luck, if you can manage to keep it up your sleeve."};
descriptions["10193"]={cn:"这个高贵的链子的来历是从科里夫·赫尔斯出生的城市传来的，他为了这条链子和他的兄弟姐妹争吵，直到最后他们每个人都拥有其中的一部分。",en:"This elegant chain comes from the city where Cliffe Heath was born. He fought over it with his brothers and sisters so much that today each of them owns one part."};
descriptions["10194"]={cn:"克里夫·西斯是个精力旺盛的冒险家。他喜欢在树林里跳来跳去，不断了解十二世界里猎手的奥秘。",en:"Cliffe Heath is known for being a tireless adventurer. Jumping from branch to branch, he quickly learned the secrets of the hunters of the World of Twelve."};
descriptions["10196"]={cn:"小心这只护符，只建议热衷于尝试新事物的人们佩戴：你多半会被恶心到。",en:"This amulet should be handled with care, and only by those who like trying new things. You could give yourself a nasty shock."};
descriptions["10197"]={cn:"荷玛尼雅天生风骚，喜好招蜂引蝶，深受男人们的喜爱。她经常利用男人们的关系为所欲为。现在轮到你了，小心她来勾引你...",en:"Hermania was very friendly, especially with the gentlemen, and she often took advantage of her popularity to get her own way. Now you\'re the one wearing the trousers, she must be beside herself..."};
descriptions["10198"]={cn:"幸运猫贵族的指环。证明你和那些肮脏的臭喵不同，属于上流社会，",en:"Lovely when worn by well-bred Ecaflips, this ring will prove that you belong to high society and are not in any way associated with those mangy Bow Meows."};
descriptions["10199"]={cn:"老猫汤姆的项圈。用来吓唬敌人不错，但是不要戴着去和姑娘约会...",en:"This necklace smells of chopped Tom Bow Meow skin. It\'s ideal for scaring off your enemies, but not so great for attracting the ladies..."};
descriptions["10200"]={cn:"地下幸运猫俱乐部成员的标志。证明你是个无所畏惧的流浪汉，而不是乖巧的喵喵。",en:"This ring is a symbol of the mangy Ecaflips club, and it will prove that you are a fearless stray, not a house Bow Meow."};
descriptions["10201"]={cn:"献给完成人生第一次战斗的幸运猫。然而西尔瓦斯特会告诉你，它并不能带来好运。",en:"This collar is given to Ecaflips when they\'ve had their first cat fight. It\'s not particularly lucky, as Silv Aster can tell you."};
descriptions["10202"]={cn:"真正热血的阿迪会不惜一切代价让火焰四射。闻闻腰带散发出的焦味吧，大量敌人的胜利希望已经被炸得灰飞烟灭了。",en:"A real hothead, Ardy will do anything to set sparks flying. Judging by the smell this belt gives off, a lot of his enemies\' hopes of victory have already gone up in smoke."};
descriptions["10203"]={cn:"多亏了铃铛不断发出的烦人声音，无论你身处何地，你的朋友们都能找到你。",en:"One of the main advantages of this necklace is that your friends will be able to find you wherever you are thanks to the annoying tinkling of the little bell."};
descriptions["10204"]={cn:"杰斯不喜欢变老。这就是为什么他总喜欢变形的缘故...能让他返老还童。",en:"Jess doesn\'t like the thought of aging. That\'s why he takes so much pleasure in his transformations, which take him straight back to his youth on a daily basis."};
descriptions["10205"]={cn:"像一个贫穷的宝藏猎人一样暴躁、倔强。戴着它，保证让你的敌人只有吃灰的份！",en:"This ring is as grumpy and stubborn as a penniless Enutrof. With a piece like this on your finger, you can be sure your enemies are going to bite the dust!"};
descriptions["10206"]={cn:"约迪·纳尔讨厌无端地把东西丢掉。事物的情感价值促使她保留着它们。比如这条腰带，曾经是她的地穴兽宠物的衣领。",en:"Jodi Nar hates letting go of items. She keeps them for their sentimental value, of course. Like this belt, which used to be her late Drheller\'s collar."};
descriptions["10207"]={cn:"呃，该从哪里开始介绍约迪·娜尔呢？她经历了很多，额头上的每一道皱纹都诉说着岁月痕迹。真有意思...",en:"Ah, where to start with Jodi Narr? She\'s lived through so much that they say she has a story to tell for every wrinkle. Which is really saying something..."};
descriptions["10208"]={cn:"拼命逗你发笑的戒指。说真的，到底谁是豆豆？",en:"This blubbery ring is desperate to make you laugh. Seriously, who came up with this?"};
descriptions["10209"]={cn:"路七法有着双重人格。他是个勇猛的战士，同时他也是个无可救药的浪漫主义者...这在关键时刻会要了他的命！",en:"Lucy Fur is known to have two sides to her personality. Lucy Fur is known to have two sides to her personality. On the one hand, she is a fearsome warrior, on the other, she\'s a hopeless romantic... which could lead to critical situations!"};
descriptions["10210"]={cn:"脏兮兮的腰带，会在你的衣服上留下棕黄色污渍。这会让你很难堪。所以你还是别带了。",en:"This mucky belt will leave brown stains all over your clothes. You\'ll have a lot of awkward explaining to do, so you won\'t want to hang on to it for too long."};
descriptions["10211"]={cn:"伊克是个脑袋跟驴一样倔的人。多年来，他始终贩卖毫无价值的东西，比如这条护符。",en:"As headstrong as a mule, Ike sometimes spent years haggling down the price of useless items such as this amulet, before selling them on to naive travelers."};
descriptions["10212"]={cn:"记住，玩火必自焚！好好驯化它，否则你会被烫死！",en:"Remember, if you play with fire you\'ll get burnt! Take your time taming this flamboyant amulet, or it\'ll give you the third degree!"};
descriptions["10213"]={cn:"阿里斯特·林头脑灵活，善于发掘财路。他的钱财全都装在腰包里。",en:"Alister Ling was great at sniffing out lucrative veins and making a huge profit out of them, thanks to this belt designed to carry kamas."};
descriptions["10214"]={cn:"这份文件授予你\"968年最佳设计师\"称号。鲁邦·豹尾为你骄傲！",en:"This document will enable you to prove your status as Stylist of the Year 968. Lupene Jaguar-Tail would be proud!"};
descriptions["10215"]={cn:"这份文件授予你\"时尚客\"称号。尼娜·瑞卡为你骄傲！",en:"This document will enable you to prove your status as a fashion victim. Nina Richa would be proud!"};
descriptions["10216"]={cn:"像新人一样猛打。",en:"To hit like an intern."};
descriptions["10219"]={cn:"和你的朋友们整夜狂欢吧！",en:"This will keep your friends on their toes all night long!"};
descriptions["10220"]={cn:"和你的朋友们整夜狂欢吧！",en:"This will keep your friends on their toes all night long!"};
descriptions["10221"]={cn:"和你的朋友们整夜狂欢吧！",en:"This will keep your friends on their toes all night long!"};
descriptions["10222"]={cn:"和你的朋友们整夜狂欢吧！",en:"This will keep your friends on their toes all night long!"};
descriptions["10223"]={cn:"和你的朋友们整夜狂欢吧！",en:"This will keep your friends on their toes all night long!"};
descriptions["10225"]={cn:"即便是再冷的笑话，它也会鼓掌。至少你再也不用担心讲完笑话后的冷场了...",en:"This cloak will applaud anything, even a badly made joke. As least you won\'t have to endure that awkward silence after yours anymore..."};
descriptions["10226"]={cn:"成长环境良好，精通十四国语言。这件披风十分善于勾引新手。",en:"Well brought-up and fluent in fourteen different languages, this cloak really knows how to make new adventurers appreciate it."};
descriptions["10227"]={cn:"双脚天生强壮而又多毛的人的理想选择。尺码众多，任君挑选。",en:"Ideal for people who have naturally strong and hairy feet. These boots were designed with an extra-wide fitting."};
descriptions["10228"]={cn:"这顶帽子专门为你量身定做。作为人类的好朋友，你的英雄事迹在附近的森林里广为传颂。",en:"Friends of the community, this hat is made for you. It will enhance your reputation for heroism in the surrounding forests."};
descriptions["10229"]={cn:"多亏了这件披风，你成为了指环之皇。很快你会发现戴戒指的手指头不够用了...",en:"Thanks to this cloak, you will be lord of all the rings. It might be funny to start with, but you\'ll soon get fed up when you run out of fingers to wear them on..."};
descriptions["10230"]={cn:"靴子的内衬严重磨损，穿上去一定疼得飙泪。他们有的是办法让你开口！",en:"The insoles of these boots are so worn down, wearing them is guaranteed to bring a tear to your eyes. Zey haff vays of making hyu valk! Zey haff vays of making hyu valk!"};
descriptions["10231"]={cn:"固执己见、错上加错是不会有好结果的。但是，有一句时间法师的谚语说的好，没有人会始终是错的，即便是破钟一口，一天也会报对两次时间。",en:"Two wrongs don\'t make a right. But, as the Xelor proverb says, no one\'s ever completely wrong, even a stopped clock\'s right twice a day."};
descriptions["10232"]={cn:"这顶邪恶的帽子会刺激你在挖矿的时候冲出去砍那些无辜的围观群众。",en:"This evil hat could incite you to hit innocent bystanders in the head with an axe as you\'re mining."};
descriptions["10233"]={cn:"作为阿玛克纳最古老的厨师家族的祖传宝物，这顶帽子闻着有一股混合了烤羊毛和猪口水的味道。",en:"Handed down through one of the oldest culinary families in Amakna, this sticky hat smells of grilled Gobball fur and Glai sweat."};
descriptions["10234"]={cn:"这双大号的靴子让你行动不便：穿上它的人们行动都很笨拙，不断的被周围的人取笑。",en:"These gigantic boots prevent you from walking properly: anyone who wears them will become very clumsy, which will amuse those around them no end."};
descriptions["10235"]={cn:"别担心你会拽过头！这件披风可以遮掩任何你释放出的有害气体！",en:"If you\'ve over-indulged a little, don\'t worry! This cloak will hide any lumps and bumps and will retain any noxious gases you might give off."};
descriptions["10236"]={cn:"珊瑚质的靴底能最大限度保证你步伐安稳，防止你一不小心笨拙地摔进烂泥里。",en:"The coral soles of these boots which give you maximum stability and will prevent you from falling ungraciously into the sludge."};
descriptions["10237"]={cn:"这件披风看起来朴素轻便：它能提高你的钓鱼水平并能增加龟鱼上钩的几率。",en:"This formidable cloak oozes simplicity and lightness: it will improve your fishing dexterity and can even improve your chances of catching some Chefish."};
descriptions["10238"]={cn:"一个骑士曾经戴过这顶帽子，它以一种不可思议的方式展现着矿石的肤质，动物的习性以及植物的脑袋。",en:"Worn by a Iop, this hat brings together the mineral properties of stones, muscular properties of animals and vegetable properties of brains in a surprising manner."};
descriptions["10239"]={cn:"能抵挡百年一遇的洪水，据说穿了之后就只能抵挡十年一遇的洪水了。",en:"These boots, valiantly designed to resist future floods, are watertight: you can wear them to splash around in puddles without worrying about getting your feet wet."};
descriptions["10240"]={cn:"这顶帽子风里来雨里去了好久，所以散发着一股泥水的清香，让你时不时忍不住挠挠鼻子。",en:"This hat seems to have weathered both winds and tides. It\'s also retained a subtle scent of must that shuffles its way into your nostrils on a regular basis."};
descriptions["10241"]={cn:"又长又丑，可以当拖把使用。如果你真的这么做了，千万不要告诉编织这件披风的治愈者，她花了很多功夫...",en:"This cloak is so long and ugly, it could easily be used as a mop. Don\'t tell the little Eniripsa who went to so much trouble to make it, though..."};
descriptions["10242"]={cn:"金匠约翰·雷侬的独创，命运挂坠是他的最好作品。",en:"An original creation by goldsmith John Laynon, the Instant Calm Amulet is one of his great classics."};
descriptions["10243"]={cn:"象征着幸运猫最自豪的身体部分。甚至能上T台上走几圈。",en:"This sword symbolizes the part of the body that the Ecaflips are most proud of. It suits them to a tee."};
descriptions["10244"]={cn:"由一位魔术师制作而成，他坚信即使在最平凡的事物中也可以找到欢乐。他制造了这把弓来证明他的观点。",en:"This bow was created by a magician who believed you could find happiness in even the plainest of things. He invented this water-based bow to prove his point."};
descriptions["10245"]={cn:"特洛菲尔是一个力大无比的骑士，举重对他来说易如反掌。然而，就像所有的肌肉骑士一样，他也没什么智商...",en:"Terophyle was a Iop disciple who could move enormous masses. But, just like all muscular Iops, intelligence wasn\'t one of his strengths..."};
descriptions["10246"]={cn:"农夫们的最爱，尤其是种土豆的。现在没有人可以阻止你种土豆了！",en:"This shovel is a favorite of the field farmers, especially those who specialize in Potatows. But that doesn\'t stop you digging up anything else with it."};
descriptions["10248"]={cn:"阿玛克纳城堡守卫在休息日的时候带着这条腰带来维护秩序。",en:"The guards at Amakna castle use this belt to contain riots and other disturbances during popular holidays."};
descriptions["10249"]={cn:"植物术士的面具，别具风格。",en:"The Korko Klako is a beautifo hato worno by the mo handso Sadido."};
descriptions["10250"]={cn:"最初用来在茂密丛林里砍树的双刃剑。有一天伐木工突然发现它是一把强有力的兵器。",en:"This double blade was originally used to cut down trees in dense forests. The lumberjacks soon realized that it could also be make a very powerful weapon."};
descriptions["10251"]={cn:"绿油油的，带着臭气。在臭气山战斗的时候会是不错的装备选择。",en:"Greenish and pungent, this shield is still a weapon of choice when fighting the creatures of Mount Stinkky."};
descriptions["10252"]={cn:"用于在牌局中为佩戴者带来好运气。",en:"This ring was created to increase its bearers luck during card games."};
descriptions["10253"]={cn:"和它的主人一样，这件披风经常被人轻视。它由绿色异种虫皮制成，质地粗糙。",en:"This cloak is, just like its owner, often underestimated. It is made from green larva skins, which gives even the nicest people a rough side."};
descriptions["10254"]={cn:"以前是治愈者里耶尔的魔杖。他曾经差点吃草莓吃到撑死，结果他失去了翅膀，疼得他痛苦惨叫，所有邻居都听见了。",en:"This wand used to belong to Liriel, the Eniripsa, who suffered a painful death from a strawberry overdose and lost his wings with a cry that curdled more than just the cream."};
descriptions["10255"]={cn:"握柄处油腻滑手，但是它看起来棒极了。",en:"This weapon\'s handle is greasy and slippery, but it does look great."};
descriptions["10256"]={cn:"园丁加斯顿·豪泽对于种植格外热心。这件武器就是证明：它总是试图耍你并侮辱你的智商。",en:"Gaston Houze, the gardener, was a little over-enthusiastic about planting. This weapon is proof of that: it tends to play tricks on you and insult your intelligence."};
descriptions["10257"]={cn:"传说中的披风。为热爱近身格斗的勇士们专门缝制。",en:"The legendary Poak Cloak was specially embroidered for warriors who live for close combat situations."};
descriptions["10258"]={cn:"威武的海盗帽，小心里面爬出螃蟹来。",en:"The Trauma is as shady as an Eraserhead made of Bherb hairs, and that\'s saying something. (If you don\'t know what an Eraserhead made of Bherb hairs looks like, refer to the great books of the Hen Pens)."};
descriptions["10259"]={cn:"用力敲一下地板（哦哦！），然后发出一声尖叫（啊啊！），法杖可以让你伪装成你梦想的人：一名伟大的魔法师。",en:"By giving off light each time you tap it on the floor (Ooh!) and deforming your voice (Aah!), this staff will make you look like something you\'re not: a great mage."};
descriptions["10260"]={cn:"在一个月黑风高的晚上，这枚戒指被偷走了。信任陌生人的代价...",en:"This magnificent wedding ring was stolen during a wild night out. That\'s what happens when you put too much trust in strangers..."};
descriptions["10261"]={cn:"健忘先生把祖传的水晶球放在了帽子下面...然后因为找水晶球而累死了。",en:"Hung \"Short Memory\" owned a Crystal Ball which was given to him by his father. He put it under his hat... He put it under his hat... and died from exhaustion trying to find it again."};
descriptions["10262"]={cn:"不断吸引周围人的注意力。",en:"These boots are so comfortable that they give the person who\'s wearing them a greater attention span."};
descriptions["10263"]={cn:"此斧可以杀猪，亦可砍树。这样的神器，不是每天都捡得到的。",en:"This axe can cut anything from a Blibli to a Treechnid in half in one fell swoop, which, you have to admit, is not something you see every day."};
descriptions["10264"]={cn:"会绕上你的脖子，让你难以喘息。是杀死仇敌的极佳武器。",en:"This wand can tighten itself round your neck to strangle you. A very notable way to kill those you have little respect for."};
descriptions["10265"]={cn:"泡泡锤的作用是发泄孩子可怕的力气，没有知道它什么时候成了装满大理石的武器。",en:"Sargasse used to belong to a child with terrible powers. No one knows what has become of this weapon since it was exchanged for a bag of marbles."};
descriptions["10266"]={cn:"射月摘星如探囊取物。",en:"This bow is powerful enough to send an arrow to the moon."};
descriptions["10267"]={cn:"触目惊心的鲜红，在血池中浸泡多年。这个款式在南瓜节聚会上十分流行。",en:"This blood red cloak has been bathing in blood for years. This type of cloak is very popular at Al Hallow\'s Parties."};
descriptions["10268"]={cn:"很明显，属于某个阿玛克纳 110 救火队员。他们用尽全力才扑灭了由一个粗鲁混蛋故意纵火造成的火灾。上面仍然残留有明显的火灾的痕迹。",en:"Apparently, this staff belonged to one of the 110 Amaknian firefighters it took to put out the fire started deliberately by the reckless Red Wyrmling. There were definite signs of arson about."};
descriptions["10269"]={cn:"杀手的匕首。拥有它们的人可以挑战最凶恶的敌人。",en:"Bashers are fearful assassin\'s daggers. Whoever owns them will be able to rival even the most bloodthirsty warriors."};
descriptions["10270"]={cn:"这个戒指是由一个丢失了铲子的埃努卓人的眼泪制造的，这个纪念品会告诉你他必须面对的绝望有多可怕。",en:"These rings were created from the tears of an Enutrof who had lost his shovel. T his memento shows you how terribly hopeless he must have felt."};
descriptions["10271"]={cn:"在械勒过往的时间旅程中铸造而成。",en:"These rings were created during Xelor\'s many time travels."};
descriptions["10272"]={cn:"这件腰带能够让你释放技能的速度加快，但也会你更加脆弱，所以小心点，别到时候把自己搞的像个兔兔一样慌张。",en:"This belt lets you fire off spells incredibly fast, but it also makes you more fragile. So be careful not to get shot down like a Wodent..."};
descriptions["10273"]={cn:"用红白相间的上等布料制成，祝你溜须拍马到成功。",en:"Red, white and very classy, this hat will make sure that all your ambassador evenings are a success."};
descriptions["10274"]={cn:"造型奇特，不是本地货。散发着布拉克玛当地独有的黑暗潮湿气息。",en:"Strangely sculpted, this staff doesn\'t come from around here. It smells of the darkness and dankness associated with Brakmar\'s old haunts."};
descriptions["10275"]={cn:"疯兔并不仅仅是你想象中的温柔可爱的小动物。这些野蛮的动物会为了一杯胡萝卜汁，用它们的盾牌把胡萝卜压得粉碎。",en:"Wabbits aren\'t the sweet, cuddly little creatures you like to think they are. These barbaric animals will crush a Cawwot with their shield, just to make a glass of juice."};
descriptions["10276"]={cn:"强大的项链，由龙鳞的残片制成，能击退敌人的精锐。",en:"This splendid amulet, made from Dreggon remains, does a pretty impressive job fighting off the majority of your enemies."};
descriptions["10277"]={cn:"如果你捡到这条腰带，那么恭喜你：这条腰带曾经属于一个世上最强的英雄。他留着胡须，魅力无法抵挡。",en:"If you happen to have this belt on your hips, you\'re in luck: it used to belong to the strongest and most seductive bearded hero of all time."};
descriptions["10278"]={cn:"曾经在餐厅里使用的刀具。因为造型怪异，老板最终决定把它们卖给飞刀杂技演员。",en:"These knives used to be used in a restaurant. Due to their strange appearance, the owner thought it better to sell them to a knife thrower instead."};
descriptions["10279"]={cn:"尽管叫这名字，这把斧头根本不能用来砍树。如果你够强壮能拿得起它，就去找只兽人试试身手，包你满意。",en:"Despite its name, this axe is no good at chopping down trees. If you\'re strong enough to lift it, try it on a Bwork and you should get much more satisfying results."};
descriptions["10280"]={cn:"由骸骨军团皮革短裤制成的帽子，能让你备受长胡子的女兽人亲赖。",en:"This hat, made from Leather Chafer underpants, will make you irresistible to female Bworks, known for their femininity, which is accentuated by their ginger beards."};
descriptions["10281"]={cn:"拉亚·比恩善于交际，乐于邀请朋友们参加化妆舞会。他经常在派对上派发珠宝，以感谢宾客光临。",en:"Raya Bean made friends easily and often invited them to costume parties. He used to give the guests jewelry as party favors to thank them for attending."};
descriptions["10282"]={cn:"从一个被爱情冲昏头脑的碎石者手中保护了克鲁姆的生命。没有人知道他能否抱得美人归。",en:"This shield has saved Kloome from death by preventing him from being crushed by a love-struck Crackler. No one knows if he managed to survive his relationship with it though."};
descriptions["10283"]={cn:"这把法杖最早由阿玛克纳农夫用来赶走草堆中的羊。你也可以毫不费力的用它追赶离群的小羊。",en:"This staff was originally used by Amaknian farmers to herd their flocks of Tabis. It\'s so light you could use it to chase straying Tabis without even getting out of breath."};
descriptions["10284"]={cn:"据说胸针的制造者是著名的铁匠布尔加。是的，就是他制造了神的武器。",en:"People say the famous Blacksmith Boulgur made this brooch. Yes, the guy who created weapons for the gods."};
descriptions["10285"]={cn:"壮丽的披风，由各种自然材料缝制而成，色彩独特，能反射伤害。",en:"This splendid cloak, sewn together from cloths of various natural materials, is unique in its color and reflectiveness."};
descriptions["10286"]={cn:"发明这把武器的匠人收了不少徒弟。他经常会想不起来他要说些什么。看起来他并不是个好老师...",en:"The artisan who invented this wand had apprentices to train. Not the greatest teacher in the World, he often couldn\'t keep his mind on what he was saying long enough to finish the..."};
descriptions["10287"]={cn:"你自己动手组装了这把弓，主要部件在阿玛克纳北部的一个小仓库里制造完成。它的质量取决于你自己动手的能力。",en:"Made in a warehouse in the north of Amakna, you assemble this cheap bow yourself. Its performance will depend on how good your DIY skills are."};
descriptions["10288"]={cn:"使穿戴者心境平和地接受整个世界。",en:"This pendant helps its wearer find peace with the world around them."};
descriptions["10289"]={cn:"很多年前在地狱的火焰中熔铸而成。你最好常备一桶水，以便随时降温灭火。",en:"This wand was created many years ago in the forging flames of Dyin Ard. You\'d be well-advised to have a bucket of water at hand just to keep control of the mini-inferno."};
descriptions["10290"]={cn:"在阿玛克纳，淘气读不进书的学生就会被敲指节，所以你会发现那些骑士的指节特别扁。",en:"In Amakna, they rap the knuckles of naughty children with this hammer. Iops fingers, you may have noticed, are particularly flat."};
descriptions["10291"]={cn:"做工精良的轻靴，能让你在战斗中行动如飞。不过你要小心严重的臭气，他们曾属于波维瑟。",en:"These exceptional boots will make you faster during fights. Sorry about the smell, they used to belong to Bowisse."};
descriptions["10292"]={cn:"黑色的牛仔帽对于老练的冒险者和风骚的年轻姑娘们有同样的吸引力。品质选择。",en:"The Clint is a dark hat, whose latest version appeals as much to seasoned adventurers as to flirty young ladies. Surely that\'s a sign of quality."};
descriptions["10293"]={cn:"受过天使雷齐尔的泪水祝福。破坏力极强，能让佩戴者挑战最危险的敌人。",en:"This sword was blessed by the tears of the angel Raziel. It\'s terribly destructive and allows its bearer to confront even the most fearsome opponents."};
descriptions["10297"]={cn:"您还记得绵球湖畔的冬雨荷吗...",en:"Help me! Help me! These were the last words LiSi spoke before the terrible truth came out..."};
descriptions["10298"]={cn:"让你看起来像是个萨弗基亚的正直国民。",en:"When used alongside other items, these Sufokian Boots will make you into an \'honest\' citizen of the Nation of Sufokia."};
descriptions["10299"]={cn:"让你看起来像是个萨弗基亚的正直国民。",en:"When used alongside other items, the Sufokian Cloak will make you into an \'honest\' citizen of the Nation of Sufokia."};
descriptions["10300"]={cn:"让你看起来像萨弗基亚的忠实子民。",en:"When used alongside other items, the Sufokian Amulet will make you into an \'honest\' citizen of the Nation of Sufokia."};
descriptions["10301"]={cn:"让你看起来像萨弗基亚的忠实子民。",en:"When used alongside other items, the Sufokian Amulet will make you into an \'honest\' citizen of the Nation of Sufokia."};
descriptions["10302"]={cn:"炼金师的理想伴侣！\n可以用来炸开路障或者摧毁已经被打开的路障。",en:"The ideal partner for explosive goldsmiths!\nYou can use it to crack blocks or destroy those that are already cracked."};
descriptions["10303"]={cn:"让烦恼连同爆炸一起烟消云散！\n用于炸毁岩石障碍。",en:"Let your worries go up in smoke!\nUse this to blow up stone blocks."};
descriptions["10309"]={cn:"你的新朋友释放着刺鼻的气味，时刻提醒着你不要忘记过往的冒险。",en:"Your new friend emits a heady odor that never fails to remind you of the wild adventures you\'ve had."};
descriptions["10310"]={cn:"这只胖芙有个大啤酒肚，高兴起来就一屁股坐地上，叽叽喳喳说个没完，烦死了。",en:"This Tofurby is so stout that he\'s most happy when sitting pretty on his rump. Unfortunately, his irritating chirping is even more enthusiastic when he\'s happy."};
descriptions["10311"]={cn:"它们看上去呆呆傻傻，你却怀疑它们狡猾至极。总之，小心点！",en:"The weird thing about plants is that they look really stupid, and yet you always have the creeping doubt that they\'re terribly intelligent. Until you know for sure, watch your back!"};
descriptions["10312"]={cn:"咕哩是理想的伴侣：他会吃掉你吃剩下的东西！还有你的家具和衣服...",en:"This Blibli is the ideal companion: he\'ll eat all your leftovers! And your furniture, and your clothes..."};
descriptions["10313"]={cn:"非得养一只独角仙在庇护袋里？请务必友善对待，不如用排泄物招待它吧...",en:"This Scaramel seems to have a thing for your Haven Bag. Oh, and you\'d do well to be nice to him, because they say he holds grudges..."};
descriptions["10314"]={cn:"也许这条变异虫是家养的，但是靠近它也会让你浑身起鸡皮疙瘩。好好照看它！",en:"This larva might be domesticated, but that doesn\'t mean that being near it won\'t give you the heebie-jeebies. Have fun taking care of it!"};
descriptions["10315"]={cn:"穿上披风，你就成为了麦田的守护英雄，为保护风车和小麦英勇奋斗。",en:"With this cape on your shoulders, you\'ll be the superhero of the wheat fields, ready to protect the millstone and the barley seeds."};
descriptions["10316"]={cn:"金闪闪的外表，让它看起来好像黄金一样。不要太高兴了，事实上它只是一堆稻草。",en:"Its hot yellow shine and luxurious finish make it look just like gold. Don\'t get too carried away, though, it\'s just woven straw."};
descriptions["10317"]={cn:"也被称作“乌鸦之栖”。这对护肩并不牢固。如果你知道正确的使用方法，也能用来吓退敌人。",en:"Also known as \'Crobak Perches,\' these epaulettes aren\'t very resistant but can deliver quite a whack if you know how to use them properly."};
descriptions["10318"]={cn:"不要戴顶帽子就以为自己有头脑了！",en:"If you don\'t have a brain, you could at least put a hat on."};
descriptions["10319"]={cn:"虽然看起来很有型，但是想穿着它们奔跑还要适应一段时间。",en:"These Getas are excellent for improving your posture, but you\'re going to need to practice if you ever hope to be able to run in them."};
descriptions["10320"]={cn:"在脖子上围一个缩水的布丁头饰，会带给你力量和智慧。实际上这恶心极了。",en:"Wearing a shrunken puddly head around your neck will bring you strength and wisdom. It is disgusting, though."};
descriptions["10321"]={cn:"当你仔细端详这个神秘的戒指的时候，会看到有一道绿影闪过，留下歪歪扭扭的痕迹和一堆泡泡。",en:"Sometimes, if you look deep into the pearl on this mystical ring, you will see a greenish light glowing at the bottom, followed by some frantic movements and a few bubbles."};
descriptions["10322"]={cn:"布丁草团对于纸球和肥皂泡有着出色的防御效果。",en:"Puddly straw offers excellent protection against paper balls and soap bubbles."};
descriptions["10323"]={cn:"毛皮内衬、温暖舒适、纹理清晰，熊猫武僧的最爱。",en:"They\'re fur-lined, snug and stripy: Pandawas love them."};
descriptions["10324"]={cn:"对于喜欢在脖子上挂小铃铛的人们来说棒极了。叮叮！",en:"Perfect for those who like to punctuate their movements with the ringing of a little bell. Ding ding!"};
descriptions["10325"]={cn:"邦塔流传着一个笑话：戴上哞哞指环，让大家来拉扯手指，好比挤牛奶，看看能从手指里挤出什么。",en:"A famous Bontarian joke involves wearing the Moogrr ring and asking people to pull on your finger, as if to extract milk, and see what comes out."};
descriptions["10326"]={cn:"任何穿上这件胸甲的人都会被哞崽骚扰。别说我们没警告过你。",en:"Anyone who wears this breastplate will be constantly harassed by young Moogrr in search of milk. Don\'t say we didn\'t warn you."};
descriptions["10327"]={cn:"让穿戴者迷失方向。你完全无法停下舞步！",en:"This mask possesses an astonishing power that changes its owners direction. When you\'re wearing it, you just won\'t be able to stop dancing!"};
descriptions["10328"]={cn:"当你躲在隐形斗篷后面的时候，这双靴子能隐去你的双脚。",en:"Polteroboots will give you the power to camouflage your feet when you hide in the thickets to escape the Boowolves."};
descriptions["10329"]={cn:"坚硬有韧性，可以用来当做划艇的缓冲垫。",en:"You can recycle Polteropolettes into funny little ships for races on the streams."};
descriptions["10330"]={cn:"没有什么比这个袋子更特别的了，然而，你接下来要做的就是把东西放进去然后带着它天涯海角的去旅行！",en:"There\'s nothing very special about this bag. However, all you have to do is put things in it and you can take them with you anywhere!"};
descriptions["10331"]={cn:"真的很轻！",en:"It really is light!"};
descriptions["10332"]={cn:"唤醒的不仅仅是味觉。",en:"This root beer loosens more than just tongues."};
descriptions["10334"]={cn:"完全不用给我看！",en:"I\'d face any tair-haur for a TAUR HAIR!"};
descriptions["10335"]={cn:"牛头人在他的一身中始终穿着同一件短衣，这是一种传统。今天穿正面，明天反着穿，如此往复。",en:"It is traditional for a Taur to wear the same tunic his whole life, making sure he turns it inside out every day, of course."};
descriptions["10336"]={cn:"只有牛头人能喝这种加倍刺激的苹朵汁而不至于把胃翻个底朝天。",en:"Only Taurs can drink this extra-strength Api juice without turning their stomachs inside out."};
descriptions["10337"]={cn:"牛头人用来敲桌子的，他们争辩的时候用它来一锤定音，定在谁那谁有理。",en:"This hammer is a Taur\'s answer to two things: putting an end to long debates and being right."};
descriptions["10338"]={cn:"牛头人都不喜欢束紧腰带。所以这条腰带显得十分宽松。",en:"The Taurs aren\'t normally know for tightening their belts. This one is very elastic."};
descriptions["10339"]={cn:"由神圣绵球的毛皮制成，仅仅依靠气味就能吓跑敌人。",en:"Rolled from Gobbsage fur, this pretty necklace will terrify your enemies with its power and smell."};
descriptions["10340"]={cn:"所有的宝藏猎人长大之后都希望过上简单的生活，这个摇篮就是见证。",en:"All Enutrofs are brought up to live simply, and this baby cradle is no exception."};
descriptions["10341"]={cn:"当心手指！",en:"Watch your fingers!"};
descriptions["10342"]={cn:"让你精神为之一振！",en:"If you\'re feeling a bit low this should cheer you up!"};
descriptions["10343"]={cn:"为你的庇护袋增添100%纯天然的气味，虽然的确很难闻。",en:"This plant emits an unpleasant but 100% natural fragrance. Yum!"};
descriptions["10344"]={cn:"从远处看很难分清是酒桶还是绵球，熊猫们每次都会搞错。",en:"It is very easy to confuse this Barrel with a Gobball from afar. Pandawas confuse them all the time."};
descriptions["10345"]={cn:"很难相信这块铁砧曾经是一块石头...看看上面的青苔！用来磨剑可不会有什么好处。",en:"It\'s hard to believe that this anvil was once a rolling stone before - just look at the moss it\'s gathered! You certainly won\'t get any satisfaction trying to sharpen your sword with it, that\'s for sure."};
descriptions["10346"]={cn:"即便是全新的铁砧，也无法轻易让你变成武器大师。",en:"It might be brand new, but it\'s not going to make you into a master weaponsmith."};
descriptions["10347"]={cn:"想发泄却找不到骑士？没事，这个沙包就很好用，而且不会叫出声来。",en:"If you want to throw some punches and there are no willing Iops about, use this ball. It feels just the same, but won\'t cry out in surprise with each blow."};
descriptions["10348"]={cn:"如果感到饥饿，这就是为此而准备的。",en:"If famine strikes, you\'ll be ready."};
descriptions["10349"]={cn:"很有限的空间，只能放几条短裤。",en:"This closet has limited storage capacity and will only manage to hold your most minimalist pieces of underwear."};
descriptions["10350"]={cn:"在庇护袋里铺上一块，顿时温暖了起来，伴随着一股牛粪味道。",en:"This carpet will gently heat up your Haven Bag, infusing it at the same time with a gentle hint of dung."};
descriptions["10351"]={cn:"警告：切勿置于高温或阳光暴晒处。（除非你想让庇护袋炸成灰。）",en:"Warning: do not expose to high temperatures or direct sunlight (unless you want to send your house up in flames, of course!)."};
descriptions["10352"]={cn:"要问为什么不是雪人？雪人会化掉的啊，雪人能吓走飞鸟吗？",en:"So what if he\'s not made of snow? This little fella won\'t melt when the sun comes out! And more importantly, he won\'t go coming to life and singing jolly songs when you have a headache."};
descriptions["10353"]={cn:"和爱鱿吸盘一样柔软坚韧。这只小玩具让人爱不释手。",en:"As soft and sticky as a Kralove\'s suckers, this soft toy will never let you go."};
descriptions["10354"]={cn:"想要学会如何编制永远不会太晚！",en:"It\'s never too late to learn how to knit!"};
descriptions["10355"]={cn:"将你的排泄物转化为芬芳的...化肥。",en:"For turning all your bodily waste into fragrant compost."};
descriptions["10356"]={cn:"即便碰到爆炸，也没有什么可以失去了。",en:"Nothing\'s lost, not even in an explosion."};
descriptions["10357"]={cn:"未来的流行风尚...",en:"Something tells you this cloak will soon be famous..."};
descriptions["10358"]={cn:"宠物装备可以于宠物设定介面中更改。此物品已无用处，可以将其分解掉。",en:"Pet equipment can be changed in the pet settings interface. This item is obsolete; you can recycle it."};
descriptions["10359"]={cn:"这份文件证明你有设计高质量\"雅号\"的能力。你曾经在街道命名大赛中脱颖而出！",en:"This document is proof of your abilities to produce quality \"puns.\" You have successfully completed the street naming quest!"};
descriptions["10360"]={cn:"和马里奥来自同一家族，这一只体型更大、更纤细，也更经常地成为配角。",en:"From the same family as the Oiram, this one is bigger, thinner and is quite often pushed into the background."};
descriptions["10361"]={cn:"放在庇护袋里，看起来就像充满消失秘宝的博物馆。",en:"Just what you need to make your Haven Bag or Haven World look like a museum full of forgotten treasures."};
descriptions["10362"]={cn:"头上戴着龙骨盔，村子里的老家伙们再也不敢小看你了。",en:"With this Dreggon shell on your head, the doddery old farts in the village will finally stop shaking their canes disapprovingly at you."};
descriptions["10363"]={cn:"没有什么比清爽的生啤更能让人忘却伤心往事的了！",en:"Nothing like a nice cool root beer on a sunny afternoon to forget your latest heartbreak!"};
descriptions["10365"]={cn:"劳动最光荣！",en:"Relentless work is always suitably rewarded!"};
descriptions["10366"]={cn:"送礼佳品...太臭了，会熏死人。",en:"This is the type of ring you should never offer to your partner - it smells so bad that they\'re likely to pass out if they put it on."};
descriptions["10367"]={cn:"仔细看！据说它会向空气中释放剧毒气体。幸运的是，现在好像不会了。",en:"Get an eyeful of this amulet! True to its origins, it would love to continue to spray its pestilent odor over all and sundry. Fortunately for you, it seems to be all pooped out."};
descriptions["10368"]={cn:"记得定期停下来给鞋子浇点水，它们会报答你的！",en:"Remember to stop and water your boots at regular intervals, they\'ll thank you for it!"};
descriptions["10369"]={cn:"无论你多么努力地去洗，你都无法去除那股要命的鱼腥味。",en:"Scrub it as hard as you like, you\'ll never be able to get rid of that delightful Snapper smell."};
descriptions["10370"]={cn:"这柄和旗鱼嘴一样锋利宝剑，能教会你鱼群战斗的艺术！",en:"With this sword, shaped like a Zordfish beak, you will master the art of Snapper combat!"};
descriptions["10373"]={cn:"邪恶的精灵，夜空顿时多了一丝邪异。",en:"Evil fairies for nights full of wickedness!"};
descriptions["10374"]={cn:"当小孩子睡着的时候，从他们身边偷来的糖果。你不知道南瓜节的习俗吗？",en:"This candy was stolen from little children as they slept in their cradles... Didn\'t know about that part of Al Howin spirit, did ya?"};
descriptions["10375"]={cn:"一个恶毒的诅咒席卷了全世界。无辜的绵球被套上了南瓜头。幸好被利用的不是碎石者...",en:"It appears that an evil curse has enveloped the World. Chunks of Pumpkwin have literally fused with innocent Gobballs. Still, good thing they aren\'t targeting Cracklers, hey?"};
descriptions["10376"]={cn:"这个棒棒糖会增加你的持久力，请有节制的使用。",en:"This lollipop increases your perseverance. Consume in moderation."};
descriptions["10377"]={cn:"你的南瓜节奇遇为你赢得了“恶灵召唤者”称号。",en:"Your Al Howin adventures have earned you this \"Summoner of Evils\" title!"};
descriptions["10378"]={cn:"有了这盏灯，再也不用害怕黑暗。它不能让你摆脱突然跳出来的潜水员，只是帮你照亮他们。",en:"With this lantern, you\'ll never need to be afraid of the dark again. It won\'t get rid of the creepy lurkers waiting to jump out at you, thought, it\'ll just light them up."};
descriptions["10380"]={cn:"小小鱼饼，给你带来灾厄。",en:"The little treat which might just be your undoing."};
descriptions["10381"]={cn:"南瓜节的晚上头戴这顶帽子可以使你与夜色融为一体。注意：在其他日子使用则有反作用。",en:"Wear this sinister hat on Al Howin\'s night and you should blend into the background to carry out sneaky acts more easily. Note: will have opposite effect on all other days of the year."};
descriptions["10382"]={cn:"如果南瓜节没人找你去聚会，南瓜可以勉强做你的朋友。",en:"A great big carved Pumpkwin that you can pretend is your friend when nobody invites you to their Al Howin\'s party."};
descriptions["10383"]={cn:"穿上这件披风，再也不用担心背后的埋伏了。但是你得小心别被门链夹住。",en:"Wear the Cwabacape and you\'ll no longer have to fear what\'s lurking behind your back. Make sure you don\'t get caught in a pinch, all the same."};
descriptions["10384"]={cn:"不要总是横着走。",en:"Don\'t let this helmet walk all over you sideways."};
descriptions["10385"]={cn:"糟糕，胸毛被蟹钳夹住了！",en:"Holy Crab, my finger\'s caught in the pincer!"};
descriptions["10386"]={cn:"清蒸最佳。",en:"These Cwabaulettes are really snappy. They\'re going to make you very happy."};
descriptions["10387"]={cn:"把戒指的名字念三遍，会看到螃蟹伸出头来搬动蟹壳。",en:"Say this ring\'s name three times, and you\'ll get to see a Cwab remove its shell."};
descriptions["10397"]={cn:"点击两下来把整组古代资源转换成新的资源。古代资源需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["10398"]={cn:"可以当做耳环，让你看起来十分有型拉风。",en:"Worn as an earring, this Cwab Eye will make you look stylish and distinguished."};
descriptions["10399"]={cn:"点击两下来把整组古代资源转换成新的资源。古代资源需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["10400"]={cn:"聚会佳品。蟹肉棒鲜艳的色彩令人食欲大增。",en:"Great for parties, this Cwab Stick\'s vibrant color will really brighten up your buffet."};
descriptions["10401"]={cn:"点击两下来把整组古代资源转换成新的资源。古代资源需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["10402"]={cn:"如果你没有脚蹼，可以试着用这些鱼鳍游泳。",en:"If you haven\'t got palms, start learning to swim using these fins instead."};
descriptions["10403"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["10404"]={cn:"点击两下来把整组古代资源转换成新的资源。古代资源需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["10405"]={cn:"传说奥古曾经用来当牙签...你也可以试试。",en:"Legend has it that Ogrest used to use these Zordfish beaks as toothpicks... I dare you to do the same."};
descriptions["10407"]={cn:"炸虾的理想选择，100%无脂肪。等等，是100%脂肪。",en:"Ideal for frying Grawns in, this oil is 100% fat-free. Oh no wait, it\'s 100% fat."};
descriptions["10408"]={cn:"记得洗净之后再塞进包里。天知道上面到底占了多少便便。",en:"Don\'t forget to wash this leg before stowing it away in your inventory. You never know how much guano it\'s trodden in."};
descriptions["10409"]={cn:"记得一定要闭上信天翁嘴。吃了这么多蚌壳，嘴里释放出的气味足够呛死你。",en:"Always keep this beak shut. After all those mussels it\'s swallowed, the smell that emanates from it may be the death of you."};
descriptions["10410"]={cn:"这个护肩是由百分百纯正的信天翁的掉落物所制成的！",en:"These epaulettes are made from 100% pure Albatrocious droppings!"};
descriptions["10412"]={cn:"在布拉克玛，信天翁羽毛生意利润丰厚。当地的居民用它来折磨邦塔国民...",en:"Albatrocious Feather trade is a big hit in Brakmar. Its inhabitants use it to torture Bontarians..."};
descriptions["10423"]={cn:"如果你虔诚祈祷，奥古也许会停止哭泣。",en:"Maybe if you ask this idol nicely enough, Ogrest will stop crying for a little while."};
descriptions["10430"]={cn:"传说植物术士阿加多曾经用香蕉来榨咖啡喝。真是个怪人。",en:"It is said that Aga Dou the Sadida used Citronana shoots to grind his coffee. Strange."};
descriptions["10431"]={cn:"这块热带的木头气味芬芳，你甚至开始羡慕木头上的白蚁！",en:"This exotic wood smells so good you almost envy the termites that are crawling all over it!"};
descriptions["10432"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["10433"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["10482"]={cn:"是的，好，可以，行，没问题...",en:"This scroll will teach you how to say YES! And, in doing so, how to make lots of new friends."};
descriptions["10483"]={cn:"效果拔群！",en:"This scroll will teach you how to strut your stuff!"};
descriptions["10484"]={cn:"有点热？无论是和一个漂亮的萨迪达少女面对面还是站在火山口，都要让这个世界看着你发光发热！",en:"Feeling a bit warm? Whether you\'re face-to-face with a pretty Sadidette or just standing too close to a volcano, let the whole World watch you glow."};
descriptions["10485"]={cn:"教会你浑身起鸡皮疙瘩，漂亮的异性会来温暖你的身心。当然，如果你是弯的就不用学了。",en:"This scroll will show you how to give yourself goose pimples, so a member of the opposite sex will waste no time in warming you up. Well, unless one of you gets cold feet."};
descriptions["10486"]={cn:"教会你如何在大家面前炫耀你漂亮的武器。",en:"This scroll will give you the chance to show off your huge weapon to those around you."};
descriptions["10487"]={cn:"教你学会闭嘴。尽管用。",en:"This scroll will prevent you from saying anything inappropriate. Use liberally."};
descriptions["10488"]={cn:"教会你无视这个世界的种种恐惧：无头兔、脱光光的兽人大叔以及腋毛长长的植物术士。",en:"This scroll will shield you from the horrors of this World: decapitated Wodents, naked Bworks and hairy Sadida armpits."};
descriptions["10489"]={cn:"教会你平息周遭的混乱氛围，使你充满领袖的魅力！",en:"This scroll will teach you how to bring order to the chaos around you. What charisma!"};
descriptions["10490"]={cn:"夸夸的必胜秘诀：出布！",en:"Theturtle\'s secret winning technique: he does PAPER!"};
descriptions["10491"]={cn:"教会你解释你胃痛的原因，以及你频繁躲到草丛里的理由。",en:"The scroll will help you explain your stomach pain and your frequent trips behind the bushes."};
descriptions["10492"]={cn:"卧室只需一平方！",en:"This scroll will teach you how to sleep standing up, discreetly and without snoring."};
descriptions["10493"]={cn:"教会你如何示爱，并且看起来不像骑士那么蠢。",en:"This scroll will teach you how to declare your love without looking like a Iop."};
descriptions["10494"]={cn:"看别人这么幸苦卖命，你就多少说点好话吧。",en:"This scroll will allow you to shout encouraging words to others while they do the dirty work in your place."};
descriptions["10495"]={cn:"碎石者的必胜秘诀：出石头！",en:"Poup\'s secret winning technique: he does ROCK!"};
descriptions["10496"]={cn:"教会你如何送给别人嘘声，要嘘得恰到好处！",en:"This scroll will teach you how to boo others. That\'s the spirit!"};
descriptions["10497"]={cn:"螃蟹的必胜秘诀：出剪刀！",en:"Kam\'s secret winning technique: he does SCISSORS!"};
descriptions["10498"]={cn:"这个卷轴会叫你如何减压，发泄之后你会觉得好些。",en:"This scroll will teach you how to decompress. You\'ll feel much better afterwards."};
descriptions["10499"]={cn:"教会你偷偷摸摸地擤鼻涕。",en:"This scroll will teach you how to discreetly deal with a running nose. In private, preferably."};
descriptions["10500"]={cn:"教会你捂住耳朵。",en:"This scroll will teach you how to cover your innocent ears."};
descriptions["10501"]={cn:"喵喵...",en:"Kittyyy!! Meowmeowmeow... Pss pss pss!"};
descriptions["10502"]={cn:"哦哦，谁是好狗？呜呜，是的，就是你，你是好...嘿！别咬我的腿，脏狗！",en:"Ohhhh, who\'s a good dog, who\'s a good boy? Grrr yes, it\'s you, you\'re a good... Hey! Get off my leg, you dirty mutt!"};
descriptions["10503"]={cn:"好烫，装备都脱了吧。",en:"It\'s getting hot in here, so take off all your bows...\nTraditional Cra song."};
descriptions["10504"]={cn:"不要被外界力量干扰了...有一天，你会站在那里，单膝跪地...",en:"Don\'t let others\' enormous power bother you - one day, it\'ll be you up there! Until then, down on one knee, knave!"};
descriptions["10505"]={cn:"脑子不够用了...老板来十个大脑，钱放这，不用找了。",en:"For the moments when you wish you had ten thinking caps."};
descriptions["10506"]={cn:"- 老天爷，森林里掉落的牙齿真大！\n- 别怕，亲爱的，别...啊啊啊啊！",en:"-Oh my, what big teeth this forest has!\n-Be not afraid, my dear, be not a... AHHHHHH!"};
descriptions["10507"]={cn:"记住这世界上依然有穷人...这不会花你一分一毫！",en:"Remember the poor - it costs nothing!"};
descriptions["10508"]={cn:"反面我们就逃。\n正面朝上的话我们就按计划撤退。",en:"Tails we run.\nHeads we fall back strategically to pre-arranged fighting positions."};
descriptions["10509"]={cn:"反面我们就逃。\n正面朝上的话我们就按计划撤退。",en:"Tails we run.\nHeads we fall back strategically to pre-arranged fighting positions."};
descriptions["10510"]={cn:"反面我们就逃。\n正面朝上的话我们就按计划撤退。",en:"Tails we run.\nHeads we fall back strategically to pre-arranged fighting positions."};
descriptions["10511"]={cn:"竖起大拇指，说“好”！是大拇指，别竖错手指了！",en:"You put your right thumb in -BIFF- oops, sorry... You put your right thumb out -POW- argh, \'scuse me... Let\'s just stop, this game sucks."};
descriptions["10512"]={cn:"先生这个是今年的新款式，只要998卡玛哦...",en:"- Aaaand for the modest sum of 449 kamas...\n- Oh, just look at it, that\'s darling, I\'ll take five!"};
descriptions["10513"]={cn:"*嘘嘘嘘* 不是我。\n...\n*嘘嘘嘘* 不是我。",en:"*pheep* Wasn\'t me. ... *pheep* Wasn\'t me."};
descriptions["10514"]={cn:"能不能把你的古尔塔给我？我跟你换，求你啦，我们是好兄弟啦！什么？别信他们，他们乱说的！",en:"- Pleeease, please please please swap your Goultard with me, don\'t be a pig, I am your brother after all!\n- What? Did someone say something? No? Must have been the wind..."};
descriptions["10515"]={cn:"...咳嗽是源自肺部不屈的呐喊，是胸中闷气不羁的灵魂。",en:"...Or how to repeatedly contract your thoracic cavity, forcing exhalation from your lungs."};
descriptions["10516"]={cn:"我感觉有点糟...\n呕...！",en:"I don\'t feel so good...\nBLEEUURGH...!"};
descriptions["10521"]={cn:"传说可以保护穿戴者免受天气变化影响，当然，对于奥古之乱你可别指望它能有什么作为！",en:"According to some legends, this ring can protect its wearer from bad weather. Unfortunately, it can\'t protect you from Ogrest\'s Chaos!"};
descriptions["10522"]={cn:"传说可以保护穿戴者免受天气变化影响，当然，对于奥古之乱你可别指望它能有什么作为！",en:"According to some legends, this ring can protect its wearer from bad weather. Unfortunately, it can\'t protect you from Ogrest\'s Chaos!"};
descriptions["10523"]={cn:"传说可以保护穿戴者免受天气变化影响，当然，对于奥古之乱你可别指望它能有什么作为！",en:"According to some legends, this ring can protect its wearer from bad weather. Unfortunately, it can\'t protect you from Ogrest\'s Chaos!"};
descriptions["10524"]={cn:"把蓝蓟和荨麻编织在一起，效果完美！再挑剔的受虐狂也会喜欢的！",en:"Thistle and Nettle fibers woven together, and what an effect! Even the most demanding of Osas will love it!"};
descriptions["10525"]={cn:"把蓝蓟和荨麻编织在一起，效果完美！再挑剔的受虐狂也会喜欢的！",en:"Thistle and Nettle fibers woven together, and what an effect! Even the most demanding of Osas will love it!"};
descriptions["10526"]={cn:"把蓝蓟和荨麻编织在一起，效果完美！再挑剔的受虐狂也会喜欢的！",en:"Thistle and Nettle fibers woven together, and what an effect! Even the most demanding of Osas will love it!"};
descriptions["10530"]={cn:"你跳的比音乐节奏更快！",en:"This amulet makes you feel like you\'re going faster than music!"};
descriptions["10531"]={cn:"天冷的时候穿出来炫耀。当心，副作用是走到哪里都会引狼注目。",en:"A beautiful pair of Nippies to show off when it gets cold out. Careful, one of their side effects is attracting attention and wolf-whistles wherever you go!"};
descriptions["10532"]={cn:"这条鱼看起来很喜欢你的庇护袋。记得经常通风，防止你的庇护袋里充满鱼腥味。",en:"This Snapper seems to like it in your world. Just remember to air it from time to time to get rid of that fishy smell."};
descriptions["10533"]={cn:"这个匕首对于止疼有着惊人的效果，非常适合那些不想听到他们对手哭泣的人佩戴，那些觉得它很有趣的家伙们实在太坏了。",en:"This dagger has the specific property of preventing pain. Ideal for those who hate to hear their opponents cry. Too bad for those who find it amusing."};
descriptions["10546"]={cn:"穿着这双靴子，你就知道怎么把敌人踢飞了！",en:"With these Moogrrtrool Boots on, you\'ll really know how to kick your opponent into shape!"};
descriptions["10547"]={cn:"穿着这双靴子，你就知道怎么把敌人踢飞了！",en:"With these Moogrrtrool Boots on, you\'ll really know how to kick your opponent into shape!"};
descriptions["10548"]={cn:"穿着这双靴子，你就知道怎么把敌人踢飞了！",en:"With these Moogrrtrool Boots on, you\'ll really know how to kick your opponent into shape!"};
descriptions["10549"]={cn:"穿着这双靴子，你就知道怎么把敌人踢飞了！",en:"With these Moogrrtrool Boots on, you\'ll really know how to kick your opponent into shape!"};
descriptions["10551"]={cn:"鱼肉是刺激味蕾的佳肴，让你尝到新鲜活力的海洋气息。",en:"Snapper Flesh is a delicacy for the taste buds. It will bring all the tastes of the tide to life for you."};
descriptions["10552"]={cn:"据说信天翁肉能带来好运。那是胡说八道。",en:"They say that eating Albatrocious brings good luck. But you can\'t believe everything you hear."};
descriptions["10556"]={cn:"一块杂鱼味的圣诞糖果！难以下咽！你吃了吗？想吃吗？",en:"A Kwismas Nibble that smells of Snapper! That will leave you licking your wri... erm, fingers."};
descriptions["10557"]={cn:"富含巧克力！（以及卡路里）",en:"Full of chocolate! (and calories)"};
descriptions["10558"]={cn:"最好的使用方法是插在头上，装成圣诞布丁。",en:"The most useful thing to do with this would be to plant it in your hair and pretend you\'re a Kwismas pudding."};
descriptions["10562"]={cn:"尽量别在漂亮女孩附近使用这个口哨，他们会认为你很下流！",en:"Try not to use this Whistle too much around pretty girls, they might hold it against you for a while!"};
descriptions["10563"]={cn:"即便在最激烈的战斗中，也能帮你保持漂亮外貌。",en:"This shield will help you stay beautiful, even during the toughest fights."};
descriptions["10564"]={cn:"把魔杖掰成两半，一半给你的爱人，另一半自己留着当牙签。",en:"Snap this in half and you\'ll have an ornament to give your sweetheart, and a toothpick for yourself."};
descriptions["10565"]={cn:"即便是平民，也能用这根棒子。",en:"You don\'t need to be a noble to carry this classy bludgeon."};
descriptions["10566"]={cn:"你就是挑战者！",en:"You are the Challenger!"};
descriptions["10567"]={cn:"旋鸟守卫军的遗物。他们成功抵御了所有敌人的侵犯，但是听到雷帝嘉嘉的歌声之後就全疯了。",en:"This hood is all that\'s left of an army of Whirlies. They stood firm against all their attackers, but lost their heads when Brrrbley Spears started singing."};
descriptions["10568"]={cn:"对着泥潭中自己的倒影孤芳自赏，你的头会变成太阳花。",en:"Spend too long admiring your reflection in puddles, and your head will turn into a flower!"};
descriptions["10569"]={cn:"这个头盔证明：闪避真的存在！",en:"Yet another piece of evidence that Dodge really did exist."};
descriptions["10571"]={cn:"你妄想在帽子里找到珍珠，却只能找到另一块鱼鳍！",en:"If you were hoping to find a pearl inside this hat, you\'ve got another fin coming!"};
descriptions["10572"]={cn:"戴上它，加入真正的素食主义食人部落。",en:"This mask will make a real vegetarian Kanniball out of you."};
descriptions["10573"]={cn:"刺鼻的气味让人几乎晕厥。几乎没人注意到，头盔的复杂构造更容易让人晕过去。",en:"This helmet smells really bad, which is a shame as everyone will be too busy edging away to notice the hat\'s intricate decorations."};
descriptions["10574"]={cn:"让你的腰部绿色每一天！",en:"Make sure you water this strip of greenery every day!"};
descriptions["10575"]={cn:"正确佩戴这款腰带，你的嗅觉将会异常灵敏。\n记得穿它之前先把自己的鼻子堵住。",en:"Wear this belt right and your sense of smell will become incredibly sensitive.\nYou should consider plugging up your nose before you put it on."};
descriptions["10576"]={cn:"看，抓到鱼了！",en:"O snap!"};
descriptions["10577"]={cn:"显然，在脖子上戴个幸运呱呱脚能为你带来名誉和运气。应该是这样的...",en:"Apparently wearing a toad\'s foot around your neck will bring you fame and fortune. Apparently..."};
descriptions["10578"]={cn:"这双钢板靴子让你看起十分敏捷，但是别指望它们能在鬼门关前救你一命。",en:"These steely boots will definitely make you look sharp, but don\'t expect them to save you from the jaws of death."};
descriptions["10579"]={cn:"只有为了崇高理想而战斗的冒险者才配得上这双靴子。宝剑赠英雄，名靴送骑士。",en:"Your challenge, should you choose to accept: to kick all the travelers\' butts!"};
descriptions["10580"]={cn:"带着自豪，穿上你的挑战者腰带吧！",en:"Wear your Lil Challenger Belt proudly!"};
descriptions["10581"]={cn:"多马西昂在本地最有名的农庄里做出了杰出的贡献。他并没有在这里呆多久。最后他留下了他的铲子，当做纪念品。",en:"Domacion became well-known for his work at the most famous farm in the land. He didn\'t stay for long, but he left this shovel behind as a souvenir."};
descriptions["10582"]={cn:"坚若磐石，让你毫无顾虑地冲向敌人！",en:"This girdle will make you as tough as a rock, so you can hurtle into anything you like!"};
descriptions["10583"]={cn:"毫无疑问，你是个冷血的独行侠。但是你难道不想找一件宽大温暖的披风穿上吗？",en:"Nobody\'s disputing that you\'re a cold-blooded lone wanderer, but wouldn\'t you like a big cozy cloak to snuggle into?"};
descriptions["10584"]={cn:"你曾是个斗士。现在，你是...挑战者！",en:"You used to be a mere fighter. Now you are... a Challenger!"};
descriptions["10587"]={cn:"愿你永远沐浴在圣光之中。",en:"Once this potion has been thrown on the ground, a light will temporarily follow the player around."};
descriptions["10590"]={cn:"首先，记得给乖宝宝送礼物！其次，记得踢不乖的宝宝几下屁股！",en:"Make sure all the good little girls and boys receive gifts! As the old wise man Expee once said, \"You gotta kick butt to make it in this World.\" so don\'t forget to dish out some punishments too!"};
descriptions["10591"]={cn:"十分脆弱，只能在一年中最冷的时节燃放...",en:"These little fairyworks are known for being particularly fragile, and only ever appear during very cold periods..."};
descriptions["10592"]={cn:"十分脆弱，只能在一年中最冷的时节燃放...",en:"These little fairyworks are known for being particularly fragile, and only ever appear during very cold periods..."};
descriptions["10593"]={cn:"十分脆弱，只能在一年中最冷的时节燃放...",en:"These little fairyworks are known for being particularly fragile, and only ever appear during very cold periods..."};
descriptions["10594"]={cn:"又香又软的甜点，巴克李的最爱。掏出你的战斧，趁还没被抢光的时候切一块尝尝吧！\n（持续15分钟）",en:"This soft, creamy dessert is Gnarled Barklee\'s favorite. Get your hatchet out and chop yourself a slice whilst you\'ve got the chance! (Lasts 15 minutes)"};
descriptions["10595"]={cn:"有些孩子喜欢先吃头，这样他的痛苦会少一点...",en:"Some kids feel better if they eat his face first, so that his suffering is over quickly... Some couldn\'t care less, because he\'s just so delicious!"};
descriptions["10596"]={cn:"一种粘稠的果汁，喝上一口暖暖身子吧。嘿，别一口气喝完啊！\n（持续15分钟）",en:"This juice is thick and sticky, but a few sips of it will warm you right up. Don\'t drink it all in one go, now! (Lasts 15 minutes)"};
descriptions["10597"]={cn:"为你的庇护袋增添圣诞气息。根据东方的风水讲究，将它面朝北方悬挂起来，来年会吉祥如意。",en:"This Kwismas Wreath will bring Kwismas home to stay. Hang it so the holly sprig is facing north for good feng-shui."};
descriptions["10598"]={cn:"肚子被塞得鼓鼓的圣诞龙鸟，厨师在上面抹了一层乳酪，闪着诱人的光芒。\n（持续15分钟）",en:"This beautiful specimen of a Kwismas Dragoturkey has been stuffed, glazed and covered in cream by an expert chef. \n(Lasts 15 minutes)"};
descriptions["10599"]={cn:"坚固的靴子，能防止在冰雪覆盖的地面上滑倒。穿上它们，可以潇洒一整个冬天。",en:"These sturdy boots were designed to avoid clumsy slipping and sliding on icy ground, so that their wearer could remain graceful all winter long."};
descriptions["10600"]={cn:"远看是披风，近看变破布！破破烂烂，布满恶心的口水，并且有多处明显的牙印。",en:"This cloak looks great from far away, but try looking at it up close! It\'s torn, covered in dried slobber, and has obviously been chewed in various places."};
descriptions["10601"]={cn:"如果冬天的降临意味着你可怜的耳朵又要挨冻了，那么可以把可怜的耳朵塞进温暖柔软的圣诞帽里。",en:"If the onset of winter means the start of an icy nightmare for your poor ears, just roll them up and tuck them under this soft, warm Kwismas hat."};
descriptions["10602"]={cn:"自尊心强的人必备：太大了，你至少会变成原来的两倍大小。",en:"This coat is not recommended for people with low self-esteem: it\'s so big and heavy that you\'ll appear to be at least two sizes larger than you really are."};
descriptions["10603"]={cn:"小小的种子，终将长成漂亮的圣诞树，如果圣诞节时在阿斯图布种下来的话，圣诞老人可能就会来拜访你！",en:"This tiny seed will grow into a marvelous Kwismas Tree If you plant some in Astrub at Kwismas time, Father Kwismas might visit you!"};
descriptions["10604"]={cn:"听说你想要个护符？",en:"Who you callin\' \nan amulet?"};
descriptions["10605"]={cn:"穿个针，引个线，扎到手，我了个...",en:"Knit one, pearl one, drop one, curl one..."};
descriptions["10606"]={cn:"你听说过小小炼金术士这个游戏吗？其实我也没听说过。",en:"Do you know the game The Little Alchemist? Nah, me neither."};
descriptions["10607"]={cn:"- 听好，我们沿着河绕过去，从正面接近他们，明白？\n- 你说什么？这么走我们会落在他们后面吃灰的！伊欧普在上，快把地图给我！",en:"- Listen, we\'ll follow the river\'s bend and approach them from the front, okay? \n- What are you talking about? We\'ll end up behind them that way! For Iop\'s sake, just gimme the map!"};
descriptions["10608"]={cn:"好吧，我们手上有些什么线索，华生？",en:"Well, well, well, well, well, well, well. What have we here ? Watson?"};
descriptions["10609"]={cn:"这根竿子的末端有个钩子，所以非常有用。这是一个微妙但有用的发明。",en:"This rod is highly effective thanks to the hook on the end of it. It\'s a subtle but useful invention."};
descriptions["10610"]={cn:"这把斧头的刀刃太钝了，如果你靠它吃饭的话，它连正常砍柴都无法。",en:"This ax\'s blade is so blunt that you couldn\'t cut wood with it properly if your life depended on it."};
descriptions["10611"]={cn:"它总是在主人的背后准备好进行偏离正轨的纸牌游戏。",en:"Always ready at its owner\'s back for card games that aren\'t going in the right direction."};
descriptions["10612"]={cn:"如果你想聊天消磨时间，这把扫帚可以24小时说个不停...！",en:"If you have time to kill, this broom will offer non-stop conversation from morning to night and from night to morning...!"};
descriptions["10613"]={cn:"所有狂热的球迷都梦想拥有一个真正的绵球球。",en:"All devoted Gobbowl fans dream of owning a real Gobbowl Ball."};
descriptions["10614"]={cn:"一个美丽的黄金喵喵雕像！",en:"A beautiful gold Bow Meow statue!"};
descriptions["10615"]={cn:"一个美丽的白银喵喵雕像！",en:"A beautiful silver Bow Meow statue!"};
descriptions["10616"]={cn:"一个美丽的青铜喵喵雕像！",en:"A beautiful bronze Bow Meow statue!"};
descriptions["10617"]={cn:"一个美丽的黄金皮皮雕像！",en:"A beautiful gold Prespic statue!"};
descriptions["10618"]={cn:"一个美丽的白银皮皮雕像！",en:"A beautiful silver Prespic statue!"};
descriptions["10619"]={cn:"一个美丽的青铜皮皮雕像！",en:"A beautiful bronze Prespic statue!"};
descriptions["10620"]={cn:"一个美丽的黄金稻草人雕像！",en:"A beautiful gold Scarecroolate statue!"};
descriptions["10621"]={cn:"一个美丽的白银稻草人雕像！",en:"A beautiful silver Scarecroolate statue!"};
descriptions["10622"]={cn:"一个美丽的青铜稻草人雕像！",en:"A beautiful bronze Scarecroolate statue!"};
descriptions["10623"]={cn:"一个美丽的黄金贝拉雕像！",en:"A beautiful gold Bellaphone statue!"};
descriptions["10624"]={cn:"一个美丽的白银贝拉雕像！",en:"A beautiful silver Bellaphone statue!"};
descriptions["10625"]={cn:"一个美丽的青铜贝拉雕像！",en:"A beautiful bronze Bellaphone statue!"};
descriptions["10626"]={cn:"一个美丽的黄金信天翁雕像！",en:"A beautiful gold Albatrocious statue!"};
descriptions["10627"]={cn:"一个美丽的白银信天翁雕像！",en:"A beautiful silver Albatrocious statue!"};
descriptions["10628"]={cn:"一个美丽的青铜信天翁雕像！",en:"A beautiful bronze Albatrocious statue!"};
descriptions["10630"]={cn:"沸水中煮10分钟。地下城冒险十分好用。",en:"Cook for 10 minutes in boiling water. This snack will come in handy between dungeons."};
descriptions["10631"]={cn:"这是干什么用的？门的绕线筒！为门铃而设的。",en:"What\'s it for? It\'s a door-bobbin! With bells on."};
descriptions["10632"]={cn:"那些自尊的人士穿着的制服。",en:"A uniform for all self-respecting Aprophetics."};
descriptions["10633"]={cn:"圣诞节来了，一定得用漂亮的圣诞树和蜡烛装点庇护袋才行。",en:"What\'s Kwismas without a beautiful Kwismas Tree spilling needles all over your floor?"};
descriptions["10634"]={cn:"礼轻情意重。但是散发着一股羊骚味...",en:"This gift might not look that classy, but at least it\'s unique. It also stinks of Gobball."};
descriptions["10635"]={cn:"看看彩色的包装盒就好了，不要打开...这样可以永远不为里面的东西感到失望。",en:"Just leave this colorful gift wrapped up and gaze at it - that way, you\'ll never have to be disappointed by what\'s inside."};
descriptions["10636"]={cn:"礼轻情意重。",en:"Well... It\'s the thought that counts."};
descriptions["10637"]={cn:"这一大堆礼物放在庇护袋里，就好想你有数不清的朋友给你送礼一样。没必要跟大家说其实里面都是空的。",en:"This big Pile of Gifts will make all your visitors think you have tons of friends. You don\'t have to tell anyone there\'s nothing inside them!"};
descriptions["10638"]={cn:"在节日里，为你的庇护袋乱上添乱。",en:"This giftwrap will add a touch of festive disorder wherever you decide to put it."};
descriptions["10639"]={cn:"说圣诞饰物没什么用的人不过是嫉妒而已，因为他们没有这些小玩意儿。快挂起来，感受节日的气氛吧！",en:"Anyone who says Kwismas decorations are lame is just jealous because they don\'t have any like this. Quick, hang it up and turn the Kwismas compilation on!"};
descriptions["10640"]={cn:"说圣诞饰物没什么用的人不过是嫉妒而已，因为他们没有这些小玩意儿。快挂起来，感受节日的气氛吧！",en:"Anyone who says Kwismas decorations are lame is just jealous because they don\'t have any like this. Quick, hang it up and turn the Kwismas compilation on!"};
descriptions["10641"]={cn:"说圣诞饰物没什么用的人不过是嫉妒而已，因为他们没有这些小玩意儿。快挂起来，感受节日的气氛吧！",en:"Anyone who says Kwismas decorations are lame is just jealous because they don\'t have any like this. Quick, hang it up and turn the Kwismas compilation on!"};
descriptions["10642"]={cn:"你这段时间打豆芙都打上瘾了么？看清楚了这只是个装饰，是假的，拜托。",en:"You\'ve spent so much time and effort thoroughly smashing and bashing the land\'s Tofus around that this hanging decoration feels like a part of the family now. Aww."};
descriptions["10643"]={cn:"虽然不是榭寄生，也可以挂在庇护袋里。如果有美女冒险者不小心闯进你的庇护袋，你可以找个借口强吻她。",en:"It\'s not quite mistletoe, but if you hang up this holly, you can probably use it as an excuse to steal a kiss or two from adventurers who\'ve wandered inadvertently into your house."};
descriptions["10644"]={cn:"为你庇护袋的隐蔽角落专门设计的花环。",en:"This garland has been specially designed to fit cozily into the nooks and crannies of your humble abode."};
descriptions["10645"]={cn:"据说起源于充满传奇的冰封大陆。人们说，只有小心照料，才会开花。当然，放在整洁的庇护袋里也行。",en:"This plant is said to have originated in legendary, snowy lands. They also say it\'ll only flourish if you give it a lot of TLC, or store it away tidily."};
descriptions["10646"]={cn:"温暖人心的画像，也能吓你一跳...",en:"This little Father Kwismas is sooo lovely, so heartwarming, that it almost makes you feel sick..."};
descriptions["10647"]={cn:"情人幽会、烛光晚餐的必备品。爱火永不灭。",en:"Perfect for cozy Descendre nights in front of the fire with your partner, this little candle is magic and will never burn out, just like your love."};
descriptions["10648"]={cn:"教你往无礼的冒险者或者怪邻居脸上扔雪球。",en:"This scroll will teach you how to chuck snowballs at adventurers who threaten you, or just the weird guy who lives next door."};
descriptions["10649"]={cn:"教会你与周围的人打成一片。",en:"This scroll will make you popular with your entourage."};
