descriptions["10652"]={cn:"让你的庇护袋里面看起来神圣一点，治愈者必备。",en:"This sacred table will look great in your crib, especially if you\'re a descendant of the goddess Eniripsa."};
descriptions["10653"]={cn:"让你的庇护袋里面看起来神圣一点，骑士必备。",en:"This sacred table will look great in your crib. Especially if you\'re a descendant of the god Iop."};
descriptions["10654"]={cn:"让你的庇护袋里面看起来神圣一点，弓箭手必备。",en:"This sacred table will look great in your crib, especially if you\'re a descendant of the goddess Cra."};
descriptions["10655"]={cn:"让你的庇护袋里面看起来神圣一点，狂战士必备。",en:"This sacred table will look great in your crib, especially if you\'re a descendant of the goddess Sacrier."};
descriptions["10656"]={cn:"献给创生之力的信徒。",en:"For those who believe in the power of Wakfu."};
descriptions["10657"]={cn:"身体一轻，头脑清醒，和死亡说再见！\n它能让你长出双翼...",en:"Say goodbye to your De Darm and death penalties with this invigorating tonic for body and mind! \nIt\'ll give you wi-ings..."};
descriptions["10658"]={cn:"往剑鞘里洒一点，什么剑都能塞得进去。",en:"Pour some of this into your sheath and you\'ll be able to stick any sword you like inside it."};
descriptions["10659"]={cn:"在寂寞漫长的寒冬夜晚，温暖身心。",en:"To warm you on those cold, lonely, frequent, endless winter nights."};
descriptions["10660"]={cn:"虽然老旧，但是前所未有的结实。",en:"This knot is rather old, but as strong and trustworthy as ever."};
descriptions["10661"]={cn:"走在阳光下几个小时也不会晒黑。",en:"This helmet will help with that wibbly-wobbly balance of yours... unless of course you feel independent enough on your own!"};
descriptions["10662"]={cn:"教会你在大雨倾盆的时候，用不可模仿的经典姿势撑起雨伞。",en:"This scroll will teach you the ancient and inimitable art of protecting yourself against the rain when it\'s lashing down."};
descriptions["10663"]={cn:"叮叮当叮叮当铃儿响叮当。",en:"Thanks to this bell, you\'ll be the star of the caroling group this year! Ohhhh Kwiiiismas Treee!"};
descriptions["10665"]={cn:"戴上它，好像戴上了牛头人的腋毛。",en:"The only helmet which will make you feel like you\'re wearing a Taur\'s armpit."};
descriptions["10666"]={cn:"为我所有！",en:"Owned by me!"};
descriptions["10667"]={cn:"你以为你拥有了它们，但是实际上你被拥有了！",en:"You thought you had \'em, but you got owned!"};
descriptions["10676"]={cn:"外形看起来朴实无华，无论怎样使用都不会坏。",en:"It doesn\'t matter how often you put this staff down, it can\'t get any lower."};
descriptions["10692"]={cn:"如果你想体验指挥千军万马的滋味，这把魔杖就是你所要的！",en:"If you\'d love to gain total control of your troops just by waving a magic wand, this is the tool for you!"};
descriptions["10693"]={cn:"呃，一次失败的手术...",en:"Ugh, a horrible reminder of a failed operation..."};
descriptions["10695"]={cn:"你能做的只有祈祷！",en:"All you can do now is pray!"};
descriptions["10697"]={cn:"和捣蛋兽的尖牙一样坚硬！",en:"These epaulettes are almost as solid as Rascal\'s tusks!"};
descriptions["10698"]={cn:"由于无数次试图咬开宝箱大锁，大牙齿已经严重扭曲变形。",en:"This amulet is all twisted and mangled because it\'s been used so many times to force the locks on treasure chests."};
descriptions["10699"]={cn:"戴上之后就像真正的地穴兽一样，十分匹配。",en:"This rascalish little crown fits you like a Drheller!"};
descriptions["10700"]={cn:"让你称心如意的披风。在地下岩石崩塌的时候可没什么用处。",en:"With this cloak, you can prospect to your heart\'s content. It won\'t save you from underground rockfalls, though."};
descriptions["10702"]={cn:"天啊！靴子上全是破洞！",en:"Golly galosh! These boots are just brimming with mischief!"};
descriptions["10703"]={cn:"腰带上的倒钩能阻止你的敌人逃跑。哇哈哈哈！",en:"This belt\'s hooks will prevent enemies from escaping your unending tomfoolery. Mwa ha ha ha!"};
descriptions["10704"]={cn:"轻轻地拍在好朋友的下面，让他浑身不自在...",en:"There\'s nothing like a little tap on the rear to make your friends feel uneasy!"};
descriptions["10705"]={cn:"嘿！伙计，今天还好吗！\n啊？你怎么跪了？难道是我的掌力又提升了？",en:"Show your friendly, manly side with a good slap on the back! \nIf your friend\'s knees buckle under the impact, you can give yourself a slap on the back too!"};
descriptions["10706"]={cn:"去吧，鼻屎君！",en:"Can\'t say no to a gift!"};
descriptions["10707"]={cn:"哈哈，别闹啦！",en:"Coochie coochie coo, little Moogrr!"};
descriptions["10713"]={cn:"每天吃5个水果和一只咕哩！",en:"Eat 5 pieces of fruit and one Blibli every day!"};
descriptions["10714"]={cn:"时间紧迫感强的人必备。",en:"Perfect for people who are always hurrying to be on time."};
descriptions["10715"]={cn:"这个戒指很懒，什么说明都没留下。",en:"Originally created for a fluffy, white, waistcoated fellow who was never quite on time for his appointments, this ring will get you up and hopping around as soon as you slip it on your finger."};
descriptions["10716"]={cn:"提供更周全的防护，同时也能让你的轮廓看起来更加圆润。",en:"These epaulettes provide a little extra padding and also give their wearer a delightfully rounded silhouette."};
descriptions["10717"]={cn:"如果你喜欢特大号的腰带，那么恭喜你，它就是你要的。",en:"This is the belt you need if you love being wrapped up in extra-large affection!"};
descriptions["10720"]={cn:"矿是你的了！",en:"The mines are yours!"};
descriptions["10722"]={cn:"和你一样友善的披风！",en:"A cloak which is just as friendly as you!"};
descriptions["10723"]={cn:"你从哪里搞到这么漂亮的项链的？",en:"Flippineck! Where did you get such a lovely neckpiece?"};
descriptions["10728"]={cn:"成为蟹中之王吧！",en:"Be the crabbiest of all the Cwabs!"};
descriptions["10729"]={cn:"请置于儿童难以触及之处。",en:"A helmet you should keep away from the nippers."};
descriptions["10730"]={cn:"我所见过的最拉风的靴子！ - 炯何",en:"\"The awesomest boots I\'ve ever seen, man!\" - DJ Gobkool"};
descriptions["10731"]={cn:"冬日里的保暖利器。",en:"This bristly breastplate will keep you warm during the winter months."};
descriptions["10732"]={cn:"朝朋友脸上扔雪球实在太酷了。",en:"Because throwing snowballs at your friends is really cool."};
descriptions["10734"]={cn:"让你的庇护袋里面看起来神圣一点，植物术士必备。",en:"This sacred table will look great in your crib, especially if you\'re a descendant of the god Sadida."};
descriptions["10735"]={cn:"让你的庇护袋里面看起来神圣一点，时间法师必备。",en:"This sacred table will look great in your crib, especially if you\'re a descendant of the god Xelor."};
descriptions["10736"]={cn:"栽下它，看小红杉树慢慢成长。",en:"Plant this cutting and watch your Baby Redwood blossom!"};
descriptions["10737"]={cn:"不小，也不够红。由两层木头构成。",en:"This Baby Redwood Wood isn\'t very babyish and it isn\'t very red. It\'s doubly woody, though."};
descriptions["10762"]={cn:"千里之行，始于足下。",en:"Exploring crypts is a real kick!"};
descriptions["10763"]={cn:"继续！年轻人，起步...走！",en:"Go on! March forth, youngster!"};
descriptions["10764"]={cn:"把你裹得密不透风。",en:"It wraps the body up perfectly."};
descriptions["10766"]={cn:"这个头盔曾经属于一位已故的革命者。",en:"This hat certainly belonged to a now dead rebuilder."};
descriptions["10768"]={cn:"快穿起来，这是你的命运！",en:"Put them on! It is your destiny!"};
descriptions["10770"]={cn:"比黄昏还要昏暗，比血液还要鲜红...还是湿漉漉的...",en:"Blood, ectoplasmic sweat and tears went into making this breastplate... and it\'s still kind of soggy."};
descriptions["10775"]={cn:"这些不起眼的小家伙往往携带着一些精巧的宝贝。",en:"These little creatures can sometimes carry some pretty refined things."};
descriptions["10776"]={cn:"戴着它，任何事都快人一步！",en:"With this, you\'ll have a head start in any construction yard!"};
descriptions["10777"]={cn:"缓解眼疲劳。",en:"This amulet is a sight for sore eyes, especially your own."};
descriptions["10778"]={cn:"神秘的护符，最好的船长也没办法释放它的力量。",en:"This amulet is so mysterious that not even the greatest captains fully understand its power!"};
descriptions["10779"]={cn:"枕着这对崭新的肩甲上睡上一觉。",en:"You\'ll be able to sleep soundly on your newly padded shoulders!"};
descriptions["10780"]={cn:"因为这对护肩，你确实配得上当船长。",en:"With epaulettes like these on, you really do deserve to be a captain."};
descriptions["10781"]={cn:"想小睡休息的时候，这条腰带可以保你周全。",en:"This belt will keep you safe when you lie down to catch some Zs."};
descriptions["10783"]={cn:"所以...它象征着刻薄、令人厌烦。还想穿吗?",en:"Sooo... this cloak is mean and troublesome. Wanna wear it?"};
descriptions["10784"]={cn:"凸显你作为一个新手的价值。",en:"This cloak will highlight your powerful stature as a young noob."};
descriptions["10785"]={cn:"闪烁着令人胆寒的光芒。",en:"This breastplate has a very unnerving gleam to it."};
descriptions["10786"]={cn:"塑形胸甲，八块腹肌加上两块胸肌足以吓死你的朋友。",en:"Pull yourself up, puff out your chest, and hold your head high!"};
descriptions["10787"]={cn:"戴上它的任何人都会变得疯狂易怒。",en:"Anyone who wears this ring will become crazy and aggressive."};
descriptions["10788"]={cn:"高贵与恐怖并存的戒指，来自于一个古老的贵族家庭。",en:"A ring as magnificent as it is terrifying, worn by the master of an ancient noble family"};
descriptions["10792"]={cn:"一次失手全盘皆输！\n- 一名失意的幸运猫",en:"One Critical Failure and all is lost!\n- A jaded Ecaflip"};
descriptions["10793"]={cn:"并非纪实：邦塔漫步\n- 巴克力作品",en:"This is not a log: walking in Bonta\n- By Gnarled Barklee"};
descriptions["10794"]={cn:"画笔断了好几枝，最终用法术画成\n- 治愈者乔治娅·玛尼作品",en:"Representation of a word, a painting with pretty brushstrokes \n- By Giorgiana Marni, Eniripsa"};
descriptions["10795"]={cn:"淘金狂潮\n- 典型的宝藏猎人作品",en:"The Goldrush\n- Typical Enutrof painting"};
