descriptions["10799"]={cn:"软橡树\n- 依据一名萨迪达儿童的天真描述",en:"The Soft Oak\n- A naive depiction by a Sadida child"};
descriptions["10800"]={cn:"两份人生，一种命运：永不回头\n- 一对孪生刺客",en:"A shared destiny, a lifetime of never turning your back\n- The Sram twins"};
descriptions["10801"]={cn:"粉色布上的黑色块：毁灭之力的具象\n- 佚名",en:"Black square on pink background: The materialization of Stasis\n- Anonymous"};
