descriptions["10924"]={cn:"只有为了崇高理想而战斗的冒险者才配得上这双靴子。宝剑赠英雄，名靴送骑士。",en:"Only adventurers fighting for noble causes are deemed worthy to wear these boots. That said, they do look pretty good on you..."};
