descriptions["10927"]={cn:"这双靴子（或者说靴子的臭气）制造时曾受过一位知名模特的启发。穿上之后你会觉得对自己充满自信，比以前动作更快，也更坚强。",en:"These boots (or their odor, at least) were inspired by a famous model. Put them on and you\'ll feel so sure of yourself that you\'ll actually be faster and more resistant than before."};
descriptions["10929"]={cn:"这双皮靴带来很多好处：增强体质，让你从头到尾容光焕发。看起来是唤兽师的最佳选择。",en:"These boots are full of wonderful things that will improve your health and make your fur shine from your ears to the tip of your tail. It would seem they work best on Osamodas."};
