descriptions["10934"]={cn:"戴上这顶奇怪的黑圆帽吧，起码你不用继续在背包里看着它阴笑了。",en:"Pop this strange, black, round hat on so you don\'t have to see how sinister it looks sitting in your inventory."};
descriptions["10935"]={cn:"插着奢华的羽毛的高帽。你只想着上位！",en:"A stylish top hat with luxurious side feather. You look just top!"};
descriptions["10936"]={cn:"用混乱牌黑鞋油打过蜡，混乱派专用。",en:"These troublesome boots were waxed with troubling black troublewax!"};
