descriptions["10945"]={cn:"刺鼻的气味不仅赶走了你的敌人，也吓跑了队友。显然和平是需要代价的。",en:"The strong odor emanating from this ring can send your enemies running for the hills... and your allies, too. They do say peace comes at a price."};
