descriptions["10955"]={cn:"和你肩膀上的杠杠非常匹配。",en:"It\'ll go perfectly with that chip on your shoulder."};
descriptions["10957"]={cn:"想拥有你自己的树模石吗？",en:"This seed is the key to having a Dendron bush of your very own."};
descriptions["10958"]={cn:"在远处看到树模石花会带来不幸...起码草药学家是这么说的。",en:"Spotting a Dendron from far off is very bad luck... at least, that\'s what the herbalists say."};
descriptions["10965"]={cn:"如果你想留住这条项链，不要把它塞在枕头下面！",en:"If you want to hold on to this necklace, don\'t put it under your pillow."};
descriptions["10966"]={cn:"既能用作凉鞋也能用作靴子。在雨天里无法保证你的袜子干爽。穿起来还算舒适。",en:"Half sandal, half boot, these won\'t keep your socks dry in the rain. Serves you right for wearing them."};
descriptions["10967"]={cn:"你知道让别人不再把你叫做没骨头的胆小鬼的最好方法吗？",en:"Who knew it would be so easy to stop people from calling you a spineless coward?"};
descriptions["10968"]={cn:"两个脑袋总好过一个...前提是脑袋里还有东西。",en:"Two craniums are better than one... As long as they\'ve got something in them."};
descriptions["10969"]={cn:"如果你讨厌骨头咯吱咯吱的声音，那千万不要选择这把弓。",en:"If you hate the sound of bones cracking, this definitely isn\'t the weapon for you."};
descriptions["10970"]={cn:"考虑到年岁久远，盾牌已经很脆弱了。它不再能抵挡攻击。主要卖点是看上去很吓人。",en:"It\'s not surprising this shield is very fragile given its age. It doesn\'t offer much in the way of protection any more, either. Its main selling point is the hostile aspect of its appearance."};
descriptions["10971"]={cn:"狂战士选择穿骸骨凉鞋来刺激自己。因为它们穿起来实在太痛了。",en:"Sacriers often wear these sandals to stimulate themselves. Because they\'re so painful to wear, of course."};
descriptions["10972"]={cn:"点击两下来把整组古代资源转换成新的资源。古代资源需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["10973"]={cn:"看起来是骸骨破坏者的骨盆！任何过去尝试探究其起源的人...最后都变成了一堆香肠片。",en:"A Chafer pelvis! Well, it certainly looks like one. Anyone brave enough to check in the past has ended up... looking like a pile of sliced sausage."};
descriptions["10974"]={cn:"点击两下来把整组古代资源转换成新的资源。古代资源需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["10976"]={cn:"梦想着坚如磐石？现在你做得到了。",en:"Want to be a solid as a rock?  Now you can."};
descriptions["10977"]={cn:"不要把这件披风留在你的庇护袋里，否则你会发现里面长出石笋来。当你后背感到刺痛的时候，你只能怪你自己了...",en:"Don\'t leave this cape in the bottom of your Haven Bag or you could find stalagmites growing in it. You\'ll only have yourself to blame when your back starts hurting..."};
descriptions["10978"]={cn:"很明显，这只戒指曾经和噬影之牙是一对。不幸的是，他们最终分手了，因为彼此天各一方。异地恋必须死。",en:"Apparently, this ring once had a bit of a fling with Shadofang. Unfortunately, they broke up because Ringmote was a bit distant."};
descriptions["10979"]={cn:"这条原装的腰带轻若无物。一不小心你会发现它卡住了。",en:"This original belt won\'t stand for any weight gain when you\'re wearing it. If you\'re not careful, you might find yourself stuck in it..."};
descriptions["10980"]={cn:"传说中的圣剑！如果你有能力将它从石头中拔出，你将成为真正的统治者。",en:"This sword is the stuff of legends! You can use it to show your enemies who really rules the roost, if you can get it out of the stone."};
descriptions["10981"]={cn:"热血勇士都爱这顶头盔！如果你决定戴上它，就准备迎接火星四射的战斗吧。",en:"Hot-blooded warriors will love this helmet! If you decide to wear it, though, be prepared for hot flashes."};
descriptions["10982"]={cn:"不断散发着热量。过冬佳品。",en:"The Lavamulet gives off plenty of heat, so you\'ll really appreciate it during those cold winter months."};
descriptions["10983"]={cn:"点击两下来把整组古代资源转换成新的资源。古代资源需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["10984"]={cn:"好像始终在监视你，紧盯着你做的每件事。",en:"This eye gives the somewhat disconcerting impression that you\'re always being watched. It seems to spy on everything you do."};
descriptions["10985"]={cn:"这些石笋实际上是石笋精的爪子。",en:"This stalagmite is actually a stiff Stalagmote paw."};
descriptions["10989"]={cn:"点击两下来把整组古代资源转换成新的资源。古代资源需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["10990"]={cn:"厚实有弹性的树叶，用作雨衣的理想选择。",en:"This thick and rubbery leaves make ideal raincoats."};
descriptions["10991"]={cn:"椰精眼睛和椰子很容易搞混。即便是你吃椰子的时候，总有人觉得你是在吃眼球。",en:"It\'s easy to confuse these Kokoko eyes with Kokonuts. Don\'t think anyone will look the other way if you try to eat one, though."};
descriptions["10992"]={cn:"穿上它在地上爬行，没人会注意到你。哦，只在跳跳雨林有用。",en:"The Skokottish works just like an invisibility cloak, in that you can pass unnoticed as long as you crawl along the ground. Oh, and it only works in the Jumpin\' Jungle."};
descriptions["10993"]={cn:"有点重的项链，带有浓厚的异域风格。如果去萨弗基亚会是不错的纪念品。",en:"This necklace might be heavy, but it\'s also very exotic. It\'s the ideal souvenir to bring back from a trip to Sufokia."};
descriptions["10994"]={cn:"有点扎手的护肩。但是制造精良，防御力极高。多么不可思议的大自然！",en:"These Ekokolettes might be a bit scratchy, but they\'re well made and offer a lot of protection. Isn\'t mother nature incredible?"};
descriptions["10995"]={cn:"雌性椰精的最爱。让她们看起来很有椰子味。",en:"Female Kokokos love this Kokolo Neck. It makes them feel very Kokettish."};
descriptions["10996"]={cn:"如果你想和自然融为一体，为什么不试试只穿一条腰带呢？",en:"If you want to blend perfectly into the background and be at one with nature, why not try adopting the Koko attitude and wearing nothing but this belt?"};
descriptions["10997"]={cn:"如果讨厌蜘蛛和小昆虫，最好别戴这顶帽子。上面爬满了异种虫和蜘蛛！",en:"If you\'re afraid of spiders and insects, this hat is not for you. It\'s crawling with Larvas and Arachnees!"};
descriptions["10998"]={cn:"由椰树枝制成，并没有想象中那么强韧。折叠一下就能放进口袋里。",en:"Made from Koko branches, this wand isn\'t as stiff as it could be. It will bend to fit in your pocket, though!"};
descriptions["10999"]={cn:"不必害怕，这条腰带记不得以前的主人。",en:"Never fear, this belt doesn\'t remember it\'s old owner."};
descriptions["11000"]={cn:"无论是谁，毫不留情。",en:"This hat leaves you no respite, regardless of who you are."};
descriptions["11001"]={cn:"如果你总是带着这个嘶嘶作响的戒指，你会发觉你的戒指总是盛满了酒！",en:"If you wear this fizzy ring too much, you may find your cup runneth over!"};
descriptions["11002"]={cn:"来，跳一个！",en:"Hop to it!"};
descriptions["11003"]={cn:"项链让你更加多愁善感，但是这并不意味着人们想站在你周围安慰你。",en:"This amulet will make you more agile, but it\'s not as though people wanted to stand next to you anyway."};
descriptions["11004"]={cn:"看！它正在生吞你！",en:"Look! It\'s eating you alive!"};
descriptions["11005"]={cn:"勿空一口气吃了太多的仙豆。他系紧了这条腰带，放了个响屁，然后坐上了那朵著名的云彩。",en:"When Sangroku had eaten too many magic beans, he tied this belt hard around his waist to plug the winds of panic for which he was famous."};
descriptions["11006"]={cn:"勿空一口气吃了太多的仙豆。他系紧了这条腰带，放了个响屁，然后坐上了那朵著名的云彩。",en:"When Sangroku had eaten too many magic beans, he tied this belt hard around his waist to plug the winds of panic for which he was famous."};
descriptions["11007"]={cn:"勿空一口气吃了太多的仙豆。他系紧了这条腰带，放了个响屁，然后坐上了那朵著名的云彩。",en:"When Sangroku had eaten too many magic beans, he tied this belt hard around his waist to plug the winds of panic for which he was famous."};
descriptions["11008"]={cn:"柔软如嫩羊排。",en:"As tender as Gobball steak."};
descriptions["11009"]={cn:"食肉植物的完美伪装！",en:"The perfect camouflage for the perfect predator!"};
descriptions["11010"]={cn:"吮指回味！",en:"Finger-nibblin\' good!"};
descriptions["11011"]={cn:"你是我见过最勇敢的人！",en:"A gutsy breastplate if ever I saw one!"};
descriptions["11012"]={cn:"饥饿的眼睛凝视着你。",en:"With this amulet around your neck you\'re bound to get more than a few glances from hungry eyes."};
descriptions["11013"]={cn:"美观的腰带，让你看起来十分犀利。除非你是个骑士。",en:"This magnificent belt will make you look super sharp. Unless you\'re a Iop, of course."};
descriptions["11014"]={cn:"美观的腰带，让你看起来十分犀利。除非你是个骑士。",en:"This magnificent belt will make you look super sharp. Unless you\'re a Iop, of course."};
descriptions["11015"]={cn:"美观的腰带，让你看起来十分犀利。除非你是个骑士。",en:"This magnificent belt will make you look super sharp. Unless you\'re a Iop, of course."};
descriptions["11016"]={cn:"让你的每一天充满芳草气息。",en:"This breastplate fills your days with a multitude of floral perfumes."};
descriptions["11017"]={cn:"很明显是从树上硬扒下来的...",en:"It looks like it was nicked while it was asleep in the woods."};
descriptions["11018"]={cn:"由树叶纤维制成。",en:"This ring is made of several leaf fibers."};
descriptions["11019"]={cn:"始终让你的双脚保持清爽舒适！",en:"Your feet will always feel fresh and moist in these!"};
descriptions["11020"]={cn:"紧急情况下，用这个戒指内含的油脂来烧敌人吧！",en:"In case of emergency, use the oil given off by this ring to fry your enemies!"};
descriptions["11021"]={cn:"虽然穿起来不怎么难受了，但是依然散发着一股猪骚味。",en:"It might not be as scratchy or as irritating, but it still stinks of Blibli."};
descriptions["11022"]={cn:"对生活要有自己的态度，不要随便卖肾。",en:"These epaulettes have a lot of attitude, and it seems they\'ve passed some of it on to you."};
descriptions["11023"]={cn:"皇家咕哩毛皮制成的披风，厚实保暖，但是穿久了会引起皮肤病。",en:"A unique garment made from Royal Blibli fur which keeps you very warm, but can cause strong skin irritations."};
descriptions["11024"]={cn:"戒指充满皇家力量。佩戴起来你会受到家养咕哩的膜拜。",en:"This ring has a regal strength about it. When you wear it, you will be respected by all the domesticated Bliblis."};
descriptions["11025"]={cn:"稳固支撑起你的躯干，没有任何缝隙。",en:"This breastplate encases your torso more firmly, because it\'s nowhere near as wobbly."};
descriptions["11026"]={cn:"纯粹由皇家咕哩碎片制成，闻起来像过期的干火腿。",en:"Made entirely out of scraps of Royal Blibli, this humdinger of an amulet stinks of dried-up ham that\'s waaaay past its smell-by date."};
descriptions["11027"]={cn:"根据苹朵的形状雕刻而成。它们并不是从树上掉下来的，你知道的...",en:"This ring has been carved out of an Api. They don\'t grow on trees, you know..."};
descriptions["11028"]={cn:"千疮百孔，半步难行。",en:"These boots haven\'t half seen some action."};
descriptions["11029"]={cn:"毁灭一切！",en:"It\'s going to destroy everything!"};
descriptions["11030"]={cn:"咕哩皮质地坚硬，十分耐用。只要毛发聚集在一起，就算弓手的近距离攻击也能被弹开。",en:"Blibli fur is extremely resistant. Once the hairs have been woven together even a Cra arrow shot at short range will just bounce off."};
descriptions["11031"]={cn:"这些金灿灿的独角仙翅膀会保护你的后背免受伤害的同时还能让你看起来很苗条。",en:"These Golden Scara wings will protect your backside and make your whole body look much thinner."};
descriptions["11032"]={cn:"一件宛如太阳一般闪耀着光芒的甲胄，具备极高的耐火性能。",en:"An armor that shines like the rays of the sun and is also very fire-resistant."};
descriptions["11033"]={cn:"这件护符象征着初升的太阳，给你带来肥沃的土地，请努力耕种！",en:"This amulet is the symbol of the rising sun. If favors fertility, but you really have to put some effort in!"};
descriptions["11034"]={cn:"印着笑话的卡牌，供无趣的人们随身携带。",en:"Cards with jokes printed on them for humorless people to carry around."};
descriptions["11035"]={cn:"好好享受樱桃的芬芳气息。",en:"Enjoy the cloak side of life, in refreshing cherry flavor."};
descriptions["11036"]={cn:"有本事你整天穿着它！",en:"Will you be capable of wearing it all day long?"};
descriptions["11037"]={cn:"即使是平静的火山，也要加倍小心。",en:"A ring made of cooled lava."};
descriptions["11038"]={cn:"从火焰中获取！",en:"Straight out of the fire and flames!"};
descriptions["11045"]={cn:"哒哒哒哒...",en:"Da do tron tron tron, da do tron tron ~"};
descriptions["11046"]={cn:"我们的目标是，没有蛀牙！",en:"You\'ll want to keep this wand in good condition. If you ever need it in an emergency, the last thing you\'ll want is some sort of blockage."};
descriptions["11047"]={cn:"戴上这顶帽子，人们会觉得你像被钓起来的鱼。",en:"With this hat on your head, people will think something fishy\'s up."};
descriptions["11048"]={cn:"这件披风的伪装功效只在晚上游泳，而且仅限于沼泽。",en:"This cape\'s camouflaging abilities only work at night, in swamps."};
descriptions["11049"]={cn:"无论暴晒多久，总是湿漉漉的。沙漠旅行必备。",en:"This amulet is always wet, no matter how many times you try to dry it off. It\'s just what you need for a trip to the desert!"};
descriptions["11050"]={cn:"鲨鱼牙齿项链实在太过时了...\n今年，请选择蚌壳项链！",en:"Shark tooth necklaces are so yesterday...\nThis year, choose the Mussamulet!"};
descriptions["11051"]={cn:"用蚌壳制成。戴上它，再也不用担心天上掉碎石者下来了！副作用是你可能一辈子都散发着一股恶臭。",en:"This helmet was made from a mussel\'s shell. Put it on and you won\'t get hurt even if it starts raining Cracklers! The chances are you\'ll never get rid of the smell, though."};
descriptions["11052"]={cn:"你会想念穿着这双靴子去钓鱼的日子的！",en:"The boots of choice for budding marine biologists, these Waders will help you blend in when standing in rock pools the World over."};
descriptions["11053"]={cn:"在任何灾难中都能让你安然无恙，肌肉看起来坚实有力。。",en:"These epaulettes will keep you safe in any clamity, and they make your mussels look huge!"};
descriptions["11054"]={cn:"现在你可以展现你的洁白珍珠了！",en:"Now you can show off your pearly white to everyone!"};
descriptions["11055"]={cn:"撬开蚌壳的好工具，不伤手。",en:"Very useful for opening mumussels without hurting yourself."};
descriptions["11056"]={cn:"有点黏黏的，并且扎手，在战斗的时候会射你一脸水，让你时刻保持清醒。",en:"A bit sticky and very spiky, this hat has the added bonus of releasing mussel juice down your face to refresh you when you\'re fighting."};
descriptions["11057"]={cn:"为了你自己着想，把上面的牙齿磨得钝一些。",en:"Leave the teeth included with this helmet as blunt as possible. Your head will thank you for it."};
descriptions["11058"]={cn:"你可以在水里穿这件披风来吓唬观光客！",en:"With this cape, you can play the old \'shark in the water\' trick on the poor, unsuspecting tourists!"};
descriptions["11059"]={cn:"小小鲨鱼，大大牙齿。",en:"Tiny little shark, big sharp teeth."};
descriptions["11060"]={cn:"由早已过时的鲨鱼鳍制成。穿上去萨弗基亚的海滩边吓人吧！",en:"These epaulettes were fashioned out of fins removed from shark carcasses. Slap them on your shoulders and get ready to terrorize Sufokia!"};
descriptions["11061"]={cn:"穿着这双靴子，你看起来像个正牌海中刑警！",en:"With these shoes on your feet, you\'ll look like an authentic crimebuster of the sea!"};
descriptions["11062"]={cn:"和鲨鱼牙齿一样锋利。",en:"As sharp as a sharp shark tooth."};
descriptions["11063"]={cn:"研发过程中，受到了一头不太聪明的鲨鱼的启发。",en:"A weapon inspired by a real ninnyhammer of a shark."};
descriptions["11064"]={cn:"就算脱发，也不要把这玩意儿顶头上...",en:"Sometimes, it\'s better to accept your hair loss than to put just anything on your head... It\'s up to you, though."};
descriptions["11065"]={cn:"在喜欢将靴子和龙鸟颜色配对的人之间，十分受欢迎。虽然已经过时，仍然能在古董店里见到。",en:"These boots used to be very popular with people who liked matching their outfits with their Dragoturkeys. They\'ve gone out of fashion now, but you can occasionally still find pairs at old hippies\' car boot sales."};
descriptions["11066"]={cn:"如果腰带不够紧，你始终可以系得更紧一点。",en:"If this belt doesn\'t feel tight enough, you can always pull the tongue a bit further. That\'s what it\'s made for."};
descriptions["11067"]={cn:"长蛆的肩垫，粘性十足。一旦穿上，就无法脱下。",en:"These maggoty epaulettes are almost impossible to get off once you\'ve put them on, because they\'re just so sticky."};
descriptions["11068"]={cn:"感受今年滋滋节的愤怒吧！",en:"This item was all the rage at the Plastronboory Festival this year."};
descriptions["11069"]={cn:"由干燥的糊糊便便制成。不推荐用作求婚戒指。",en:"This ring was sculpted from dried Mushd droppings. We don\'t recommend you use it for marriage proposals."};
descriptions["11070"]={cn:"洗完脸后带上，能让皮肤细腻红润有光泽。",en:"If you put the mask on right after cleansing, it will make you skin soft and radiant."};
descriptions["11071"]={cn:"为任何有自尊的滋滋度身定做！",en:"A luxury belt for any self-respecting boo!"};
descriptions["11072"]={cn:"注意：接触敏感皮肤易导致皮疹，穿戴前请使用防护霜。",en:"Warning: Contact with sensitive skins may cause hives. You should apply cream before use."};
descriptions["11073"]={cn:"多触手的护符，能治愈部分病痛，例如晕船以及海鲜中毒！",en:"This tentacular amulet can cure certain illnesses, most notably sea sickness and sea food poisoning!"};
descriptions["11074"]={cn:"弹力十足的胸甲，无论你是高矮胖瘦，都不用再去考虑其他型号。",en:"This breastplate\'s flexibility will allow you to go from a heavyweight to a lightweight (or vice-versa) without the shame of having to buy a different size."};
descriptions["11075"]={cn:"如果你把它当腰带用，你必须得小心了。万一你惹恼了它，就再也取不下这条腰带，在你毫不知情的情况下，裤子会突然脱落。",en:"If you\'re using this tentacle as a belt, you\'re going to have to be nice to it. If you annoy it, it won\'t waste any time untying itself and you\'ll be caught with your trousers down before you know it."};
descriptions["11076"]={cn:"由爱鱿触手制成，内衬防滑护垫。",en:"These boots have anti-skid soles, made from real Kralove tentacles."};
descriptions["11077"]={cn:"噗噗...它在水里...",en:"Plop... it\'s in the water..."};
descriptions["11078"]={cn:"含有爱鱿触手纤维的松木魔杖。",en:"A cedar wand which contains a Krala tentacle fiber."};
descriptions["11079"]={cn:"此物品已无功用。",en:"This item is no longer functional."};
descriptions["11080"]={cn:"此物品已无功用；使用（点击两下）来回收制作这件物品的资源。",en:"This item is no longer functional; use it (by double-clicking on it) to collect the ingredients used to craft it."};
descriptions["11081"]={cn:"此物品已无功用；使用（点击两下）来回收制作这件物品的资源。",en:"This item is no longer functional; use it (by double-clicking on it) to collect the ingredients used to craft it."};
descriptions["11082"]={cn:"此物品已无功用；使用（点击两下）来回收制作这件物品的资源。",en:"This item is no longer functional; use it (by double-clicking on it) to collect the ingredients used to craft it."};
descriptions["11083"]={cn:"此物品已无功用；使用（点击两下）来回收制作这件物品的资源。",en:"This item is no longer functional; use it (by double-clicking on it) to collect the ingredients used to craft it."};
descriptions["11084"]={cn:"我叫你不要乱扔东西嘛！乱扔东西是不对的...斧子是兵器，乱扔会污染环境的，砸到了小朋友怎么办？就算砸不到小朋友砸到花花草草也不好嘛...",en:"You can\'t just throw it around carelessly. It can do a lot of damage, you know, even to you."};
descriptions["11085"]={cn:"梦想成真！你终于可以变身章鱼了！",en:"Have you always dreamed of looking like an octopus? Now you can!"};
descriptions["11101"]={cn:"棕色的物质，让你毫无食欲。但是我保证，它味道棒极了！",en:"This brownish substance will probably put you off your food, but it tastes delicious, I swear!"};
descriptions["11102"]={cn:"高热量食物。每天吃的话，保证你增肥一圈。",en:"Every spoonful of this spread is chock-full of calories. Use it as the basis of your new diet and you\'re guaranteed to gain one dress size per month!"};
descriptions["11103"]={cn:"椰子充满了神秘。唯一可以肯定的是，如果上面有三个洞，那肯定是用来塞手指的。",en:"The Kokonut is quite a mystery. The only thing we know for sure about it is that if it has three holes, they must be to put your fingers in."};
descriptions["11104"]={cn:"椰汁的诱人气味，促使你忍不住想喝上几口。小心，会把你的牙齿粘在一起！",en:"The strong smell of Kokonut coming from this sap will probably make you want to put it in your mouth. Careful, though, as it\'ll most likely stick your teeth together!"};
descriptions["11105"]={cn:"好脆弱，一棍子就能敲断。",en:"Can be broken by sticks and stones."};
descriptions["11106"]={cn:"由腿骨粉末制成。经过长年累月的战斗洗礼，它们已经被磨成烂泥。",en:"This flour is made from old Chafer Bones which have been reduced to mush by years of fighting... and swords."};
descriptions["11107"]={cn:"他们曾经说“Ni！”现在他们说：“Ekki-Ekki-Ekki-Ekki-PTANG。Zoom-Boing。Z\'nourrwringmm！”奇怪...",en:"They used to say \"Ni!\" Now they say \"Ekki-Ekki-Ekki-Ekki-PTANG. Zoom-Boing. Z\'nourrwringmm!\" Strange..."};
descriptions["11108"]={cn:"他们曾经说“Ni！”现在他们说：“Ekki-Ekki-Ekki-Ekki-PTANG。Zoom-Boing。Z\'nourrwringmm！”奇怪...",en:"They used to say \"Ni!\" Now they say \"Ekki-Ekki-Ekki-Ekki-PTANG. Zoom-Boing. Z\'nourrwringmm!\" Strange..."};
descriptions["11109"]={cn:"他们曾经说“Ni！”现在他们说：“Ekki-Ekki-Ekki-Ekki-PTANG。Zoom-Boing。Z\'nourrwringmm！”奇怪...",en:"They used to say \"Ni!\" Now they say \"Ekki-Ekki-Ekki-Ekki-PTANG. Zoom-Boing. Z\'nourrwringmm!\" Strange..."};
descriptions["11110"]={cn:"漂亮的肩甲，和红辣椒完美搭配。如果你能找到任何一个，那简直是...",en:"These pretty epaulettes would go quite well with chili. If you can find any, that is..."};
