descriptions["11113"]={cn:"外形看起来好像你随身携带的钱包。当你输掉战斗的时候，可以装作你勇敢战斗过的样子。",en:"These epaulettes shaped like a purse will carry your makeup everywhere you go. Very helpful for putting on a brave face when you lose."};
