descriptions["11131"]={cn:"为频繁放弃战斗的人特意准备，并不会让你变得更勇敢，只是让你更善于逃命！",en:"All those who continually flee fights, this is the wand for you. It won\'t actually make you any braver, but it will make you better at running away!"};
