descriptions["11266"]={cn:"任何一个名符其实的宝藏猎人都留着满脸的胡子，老克里·诺希夫也不例外。有一天他的妻子，诺希夫太太为他买了一把剃须刀，他觉得还是拿来当作武器比较好...",en:"Any Enutrof worthy of the name has a beard, and old Krys Nosheive was no exception. One day his wife, Mrs Nosheive, bought him a razor, and he decided he would rather use it as a weapon..."};
