descriptions["11278"]={cn:"由伟大的卡尔·格劳乔制造，他是痞子联盟的守护者。他在他的墓碑上刻上了他的名言“经验使人上瘾”。",en:"This sword was made by the great Karl Groucho, defender of the Hoglians. He engraved his famous maxim in its side: \"XP is the opium of the people.\""};
descriptions["11279"]={cn:"由伟大的卡尔·格劳乔制造，他是痞子联盟的守护者。他在他的墓碑上刻上了他的名言“经验使人上瘾”。",en:"This sword was made by the great Karl Groucho, defender of the Hoglians. He engraved his famous maxim in its side: \"XP is the opium of the people.\""};
descriptions["11280"]={cn:"由伟大的卡尔·格劳乔制造，他是痞子联盟的守护者。他在他的墓碑上刻上了他的名言“经验使人上瘾”。",en:"This sword was made by the great Karl Groucho, defender of the Hoglians. He engraved his famous maxim in its side: \"XP is the opium of the people.\""};
descriptions["11281"]={cn:"出发去新世界做任务？即便仅仅是为了外观因素，也不要忘了带这顶无价的帽子。",en:"Off on a quest for the New World? Don\'t forget this priceless Pioneer Hat, even if it\'s just to look snazzy."};
descriptions["11282"]={cn:"老实说，这件披风并不提供任何独特的东西。但是闭上眼睛，想象一下，你可以在脑海中把它想成任何你喜欢的东西！",en:"To be honest this cape doesn\'t really offer anything unique. But with a little imagination, you can make it into anything you like!"};
descriptions["11283"]={cn:"新一代革命性产品，既防水又能载歌载舞的先驱靴。有了它们，你能轻易征服十二世界中的天堑地沟。",en:"Here you have the revolutionary, first-of-their-kind, waterproof, all-singing, all-dancing Pioneer Boots. With these on, you\'ll be able to rise above most situations in the World of Twelve."};
descriptions["11284"]={cn:"微微闪烁着阳光的肩甲，甚至能将执政官推进阴影之中。",en:"These epaulettes, which subtly reflect rays of sunshine, have got what it takes to put even the Governor in the shade."};
descriptions["11285"]={cn:"可以用来猎杀绵球、投降或者引起某人的注意...先驱旗帜是真正冒险者的必备品！",en:"You can use it to fend off Gobballs, call a truce, or get someone\'s attention - the Pioneer Flag is a must-have for all true adventurers!"};
descriptions["11286"]={cn:"拉开点，再拉开点！打开之后你就会变成魔戒使者。当然，也许不会...",en:"Scroll up, scroll up! Open up this scroll and you might just become a ringmaster. Then again, you might not..."};
descriptions["11287"]={cn:"先来先得！别人还在吃奶的时候你已经征服过世界了，尽管自豪吧！\n灭哈哈哈哈！",en:"First come, first served! Display this proudly to show all the others that you were here to conquer the World before them! Nah nah na-nah naaah!"};
descriptions["11288"]={cn:"神灵赐予了你称号，证明你挺身而出，拯救世界的丰功伟绩。",en:"This title, given by the gods, will remind other adventurers that you were among the first to try and save your World!"};
descriptions["11289"]={cn:"世界头号歼灭者就是你啦！",en:"Prove to the World that you are its best eradictor!"};
descriptions["11290"]={cn:"蚊子杀杀杀！",en:"Now all the Boowolves think you\'re pretty fly, for a nice guy."};
descriptions["11291"]={cn:"没什么好看的，却很讨时间法师喜欢。好好欣赏他们缠着绷带兜风的傻样吧。",en:"This cloak isn\'t much to look at, but Xelors certainly have more than enough time for it. Just watch them prancing about in this horrendous garment."};
descriptions["11292"]={cn:"只有当你蠢得像个孩子一样，头被砸到的时候，才有必要戴这顶帽子。\n不是的？哦...好吧...我很抱歉...",en:"If you wear a helmet like this, it\'s because you were probably dropped on your head as a child.\nOh wait... Oh... well... I... urm... sorry..."};
descriptions["11293"]={cn:"什么，你说我的胸甲是用厕纸做的？",en:"What do you mean my breastplate is made of toilet paper? My breastplate is not made of toilet paper!"};
descriptions["11294"]={cn:"拉一拉带子就可以轻松绊倒穿着这双靴子的人。下一场战斗说不定会十分有意思...",en:"You just need to pull on the straps to trip up whoever is wearing these boots. The next battle might wind up to be a funny one..."};
descriptions["11296"]={cn:"耳后略感潮湿。",en:"This hat might make you slightly wet behind the ears."};
descriptions["11297"]={cn:"你汗流如雨，仿佛一个真正的勇士！",en:"Your head gets pretty sweaty under this helmet, but that\'s okay - it makes you feel like an authentic warrior!"};
descriptions["11298"]={cn:"这顶透气舒适的帽子让你一整天心情愉快。别扭头过度。把脖子扭坏了就不好了。",en:"This well-ventilated hat will keep you feeling fresh all day long. Watch out for the draft, however. You don\'t want to wind up with a bad neck!"};
descriptions["11299"]={cn:"坚硬如石头一般，戴上它就没人敢碰你了。不过戴着的时候千万别做事做得头都大了，那样就拿不下来了。",en:"Solid, solid as a rock. This hat makes you almost untouchable. But don\'t get big-headed or you won\'t be able to put it on again."};
descriptions["11300"]={cn:"美观优雅的披风，吸水性好。它会给你带来好运，但是不幸的是，它会变得沉重、潮湿又难闻，简直无法上身。",en:"Keep your ahead above water with this elegant cape. It will bring you good luck but unfortunately it quickly becomes very heavy, wet, smelly, soggy, and incredibly difficult to wear. It never rains but pours, huh?"};
descriptions["11301"]={cn:"炽热的披风，十分漂亮。另有石棉内衣单独销售。",en:"A fiery cloak that\'ll go with your hot-headed nature and make you look all the more imposing! Asbestos underwear sold separately."};
descriptions["11302"]={cn:"这件披风提供很少的抗风力，能让你在敌人攻击下获得喘息之机。",en:"This cape offers very little protection against the wind, This cape offers very little protection against the wind, but may allow you to breeze by some attacks."};
descriptions["11303"]={cn:"呜哈，看我烂泥做的披风。看那些碎石者都羡慕死了！",en:"Woah, a cape made of earth. You certainly know how to make a Crackler jealous!"};
descriptions["11304"]={cn:"你可以从靴子里往外倒水，但是小心了，没有使用说明，在鞋跟上也没有。",en:"You might be able to pour water out of these boots, but be careful: there are no instructions, not even on the heel."};
descriptions["11305"]={cn:"觉得自己行走在火炉上？确实是这样。起码这样能让你走得更快！",en:"Feel like you\'re walking on burning embers? That\'s because you are. At least it makes you run faster!"};
descriptions["11306"]={cn:"世界上最舒适的鞋子在你脚下，你觉得就像在第七天堂飞驰！听起来很美好吧？",en:"The most comfortable boots in the World are at your feet! You\'ll feel like you\'re walking on seventh Incarnam. Doesn\'t that sound heavenly?"};
descriptions["11307"]={cn:"一双带着泥泞的的靴子。被人欺负了，你就踢他屁股，让他光鲜笔挺的裤子上沾满泥水，报仇的感觉真舒服...",en:"These somewhat muddy boots will allow you to put stains on your enemy\'s freshly-starched linen pants after he kicks your butt. Revenge is oh so sweet..."};
descriptions["11308"]={cn:"无论大雨倾盆还是烈日曝晒，这对肩甲会保护你左右，带你穿越地狱，踏平怒涛。",en:"These epaulettes will protect you come rain or shine, through hell or high water."};
descriptions["11309"]={cn:"你肩膀上烫得已经可以煎牛排了。",en:"When you asked your god to make you hot, you didn\'t really mean this, but it\'s not all bad - your shoulders are so sizzling you can fry Boowolf steaks on them, so you\'re the most popular adventurer in town!"};
descriptions["11310"]={cn:"这对肩甲轻如扬尘，穿戴起来不费吹灰之力。当心别让风吹走了，引得人群看着你狼狈的样子哄笑。",en:"You certainly won\'t huff and puff about the weight of these Epaulettes - they\'re as light as air. Just make sure they don\'t blow away or there\'ll be gales of laughter and you\'ll be left breathless."};
descriptions["11311"]={cn:"这件矿石护肩富含健康所需的各种矿物质，实际上哞哞就很喜欢舔它，你要在动物圈子里出名了！",en:"These epaulettes, rich in minerals, are a great source of healthy nutrients. In fact, the Moogrrs love licking them. You\'re going to be very popular!"};
descriptions["11314"]={cn:"融合了所有元素的力量，大量的知识灌进你的脑袋。起码你要记得目的地的位置，然后给敌人一个狠狠的头槌！",en:"This helmet combines the power of all the elements, which will unfortunately overwhelm you with knowledge. Make sure you know where you\'re going and be sure to attack your enemy head on!"};
descriptions["11315"]={cn:"气味、外观以及手感都无可挑剔...你都不好意思穿了。",en:"It smells good, looks good, feels good... It\'s almost a shame to wear it."};
descriptions["11316"]={cn:"十分贴合原拥有者的脚型。但愿不是二手货，否则就有点尴尬了...",en:"These boots adapt perfectly to the morphology of their original owner. Here\'s hoping they\'re not second hand or you might find yourself feeling a bit uncomfortable."};
descriptions["11317"]={cn:"与任何服饰都能完美搭配！你的衣橱里也应该有一件！",en:"These epaulettes go well with almost everything! It\'s great to have wardrobe staples like these."};
descriptions["11318"]={cn:"哦哦哦，看看这只小啾啾！颜色很漂亮，不是吗？哦哦...他拉的便便颜色也很漂亮...",en:"Bawww, look at the little Piwi! Who\'s a colorful boy, hmm? Oh... and he does colorful droppings too..."};
descriptions["11319"]={cn:"这份文件授予你\"969年度阿玛克纳最佳\"称号。蕾顿·麦克艾伦为你骄傲！",en:"This document enables you to claim the title of Miss or Mister Amakna 969. Yungold McFroggileg would be so proud of you!"};
descriptions["11320"]={cn:"这份文件授予你\"969年度邦塔最佳\"称号。蕾顿·麦克艾伦为你骄傲！",en:"This document enables you to claim the title of Miss or Mister Bonta 969. Yungold McFroggileg would be so proud of you!"};
descriptions["11321"]={cn:"这份文件授予你\"969年度布拉克玛最佳\"称号。蕾顿·麦克艾伦为你骄傲！",en:"This document enables you to claim the title of Miss or Mister Brakmar 969. Yungold McFroggileg would be so proud of you!"};
descriptions["11322"]={cn:"这份文件授予你\"969年度萨弗基亚最佳\"称号。蕾顿·麦克艾伦为你骄傲！",en:"This document enables you to claim the title of Miss or Mister Sufokia 969. Yungold McFroggileg would be so proud of you!"};
descriptions["11323"]={cn:"这份文件授予你\"969年度十二世界最佳\"称号。蕾顿·麦克艾伦为你骄傲！",en:"This document enables you to claim the title of Miss or Mister World of Twelve 969. Yungold McFroggileg would be so proud of you!"};
