descriptions["11332"]={cn:"旗帜挥起来啊！",en:"Put the Flags Out! the Pioneer Flag is a must-have for all true adventurers!"};
descriptions["11333"]={cn:"久经时间冲刷的贝壳。",en:"This old shell traveled back and forth with the tides for centuries before finishing up in a Mollusky\'s belly."};
descriptions["11334"]={cn:"有没有人跟你说过你有一颗热爱鱿鱼的心？",en:"Has anyone ever told you that you have the heart of a Kralove?"};
descriptions["11335"]={cn:"自从这颗大牙齿在《大白鲨》上露过脸之后，它就不停地到处吹嘘。",en:"Ever since this tooth landed a cameo in cult film Jaw, it won\'t stop bragging about it and humming the theme tune."};
descriptions["11336"]={cn:"空荡荡的贝壳，有股蚌类的腥味。",en:"An empty shell which smells of old mussels. Nice..."};
descriptions["11337"]={cn:"油炸特别好吃。如果要凑齐一顿大餐的量可能有点难...你必须击败一群软体动物！",en:"Mussels like this one are delicious with fries. Good luck getting enough of them for a meal though - you\'ll have to battle a whole horde of Molluskies!"};
descriptions["11338"]={cn:"看起来很脆弱，踩一脚能疼死你。",en:"This spike may look fragile, but it hurts like a mofo if you stand on it."};
descriptions["11339"]={cn:"呵呵...轻拍它的表面，引起一阵荡漾。",en:"Hehe... When you tap its surface, it goes blubbalubbalubbalubbalub."};
descriptions["11341"]={cn:"鲨鱼皮很厚实，缺点是油腻、沉重又滑手。",en:"Shark skin is known for being very thick. Unfortunately, it\'s also very greasy, very heavy and very slippery."};
descriptions["11342"]={cn:"在穿上它游泳的时候，起身突然发现周围没人了，不要觉得奇怪。如果真的碰到鲨鱼了，请自救！",en:"If you\'re swimming around with this on your head, then don\'t be surprised if you find yourself all alone in the pool. If you meet a real shark, then SWIM FOR YOUR LIFE!"};
descriptions["11343"]={cn:"转为热心的测试者准备。",en:"For nice testers"};
descriptions["11345"]={cn:"转为热心的测试者准备。",en:"For playful testers"};
descriptions["11349"]={cn:"这顶帽子真会令你挠头...那些恼人的碎屑哪儿来的？",en:"This hat will really have you scratching your head... Where are all those irritating crumbs coming from?"};
descriptions["11350"]={cn:"这顶帽子真会令你挠头...那些恼人的碎屑哪儿来的？",en:"This hat will really have you scratching your head... Where are all those irritating crumbs coming from?"};
descriptions["11351"]={cn:"这顶帽子真会令你挠头...那些恼人的碎屑哪儿来的？",en:"This hat will really have you scratching your head... Where are all those irritating crumbs coming from?"};
descriptions["11352"]={cn:"这顶帽子真会令你挠头...那些恼人的碎屑哪儿来的？",en:"This hat will really have you scratching your head... Where are all those irritating crumbs coming from?"};
descriptions["11353"]={cn:"值得自豪的称号，阿玛拉万岁！",en:"A new title that you can really be proud of. Long live Amara!"};
descriptions["11354"]={cn:"一个值得自豪的新称号。艾尔伯万岁！",en:"A new title that you can really be proud of. Long live Elbor!"};
descriptions["11355"]={cn:"根据一个传奇治愈者的描述，这块巧克力蕴含巨大能量。咬一口可以让你从林黛玉变身方世玉！",en:"According to an Eniripsa legend, this chocolate is a brilliant aphrodisiac. This heart will put you in all kinds of states!"};
descriptions["11356"]={cn:"治愈者们团结一心，制造了这些白如初雪的烟火来庆祝圣巧克力节。",en:"The Eniripsas banded together to create these pure-as-snow white Fairyworks to celebrate Ballotwine\'s Day."};
descriptions["11357"]={cn:"治愈者们团结一心，制造了这些红色烟火来庆祝圣巧克力节。",en:"The Eniripsas banded together to create these fiery red Fairyworks to celebrate Ballotwine\'s Day."};
descriptions["11358"]={cn:"治愈者们团结一心，制造了这些粉色烟火来庆祝圣巧克力节。",en:"The Eniripsas banded together to create these candy-floss pink Fairyworks to celebrate Ballotwine\'s Day."};
descriptions["11359"]={cn:"很甜很粘牙，别吃太多。\n（持续15分钟）",en:"A too sweet, too sticky, too toffee-y candy. \n(Lasts 15 minutes)"};
descriptions["11360"]={cn:"显然，每个人都知道里面有什么，但是没人愿意说出来。好好享受！\n（持续15分钟）",en:"Apparently everybody knows what\'s in it, but nobody wants to say it out loud. Bon appétit!\n(Lasts 15 minutes)"};
descriptions["11361"]={cn:"舔它，捏它，拆开它，嚼碎它，分享它，吞掉它：做什么你都爱随身携带它，因为它的口味经久不衰！\n（持续15分钟）",en:"Lick it, twist it, untwist it, chew it, share it, bop it: do what you like with it, because the taste will stay the same!\n(Lasts 15 minutes)"};
descriptions["11362"]={cn:"敲成碎片才好吃！\n（持续15分钟）",en:"With a little bit of brute force you\'ll be able to break this little heart into smithereens, which somehow makes it even tastier!\n(Lasts 15 minutes)"};
descriptions["11363"]={cn:"玫瑰稀有，极致浪漫。生活多美好！",en:"This bouquet of extremely rare eternal roses is beyond romantic. It\'s everything you need to light up people\'s hearts."};
descriptions["11364"]={cn:"因为稀有，所以珍贵。值得一生珍藏。千万不要贱卖给宝藏猎人。",en:"Due to its unimaginable rarity, this ring is far from being on the cheap side. Hold on to it for dear life and do not sell it to an Enutrof for love nor money."};
descriptions["11365"]={cn:"红颜色的啾啾蓝颜色的咕，什么颜色的绵球最呀最幸福。",en:"Piwis are red, Googoos are blue, show me some love and I\'ll share my Wakfu."};
descriptions["11366"]={cn:"快到碗里来！",en:"For healthy development and lip-smacking cavities! Sweet!"};
descriptions["11368"]={cn:"熊猫武僧慷慨分享，让你可以看清熊猫武僧的眼里的秘密。永远别对熊猫武僧说不！\n（持续15分钟）",en:"Generously shared by Pandawas, this root beer will allow you to see things through their eyes. Never say no to a Pandawa! \n(Lasts 15 minutes)"};
descriptions["11369"]={cn:"三叶草啤酒最佳伴侣，带出珍贵的风味。随意享用。\n（持续1场战斗）",en:"These divine little biscuits go hand in hand with Clover Root Beer to really bring out those precious flavors and zests. Consume liberally. \n(Lasts 1 combat)"};
descriptions["11370"]={cn:"在圣三叶草节那天，到处都是这种四片叶子的草，很显然，没什么幸运可言。",en:"These things are all over the place around Saint Potrick\'s Day. Obviously, they\'re not lucky."};
descriptions["11371"]={cn:"漂亮的帽子，酒鬼的最爱。如果你戴的时间太长会让你的脑袋受伤。",en:"This wonderful hat, adored by revelers, hurts your head if you wear it for too long."};
descriptions["11372"]={cn:"传说这件披风会带给你好运和大桶金币。注意：会缩水。",en:"According to the legend, this cloak will bring you luck and pots of gold. It\'s your choice!"};
descriptions["11373"]={cn:"很明显你有福了。",en:"Obviously this title is going to bring you luck."};
descriptions["11374"]={cn:"圣伯特里克节日上的简易实用的木桶。不幸的是，桶底有个小洞，而且附近没有稻草、斧子或者小石子什么的...",en:"A very handy, wooden bucket just for Saint Potrick\'s. Unfortunately, there\'s a hole in the bucket and no straw, axes or stones in sight."};
descriptions["11375"]={cn:"春天来临的时候，胡萝卜会长得到处都是...就像兔兔一样！细心整理一下，这束胡萝卜会散发出奇异的香气。",en:"When spring arrives, Cawwots start springing up from nowhere - much like Wodents! Carefully arranged, this bouquet exudes a wondrous aroma."};
descriptions["11376"]={cn:"不同于真正的绵绵，这只绵绵气味好闻多了！\n（持续15分钟）",en:"Unlike the real thing, this Gobbly smells lovely!\n(Lasts 15 minutes)"};
descriptions["11377"]={cn:"村里的土豪一定会说“哈，看来你终于找到了一个和你旗鼓相当的怪物。”也许他只是出于嫉妒才这么说的，因为他自己没有。\n（持续15分钟）",en:"The village bully will probably say, \"Ha, looks like you\'ve finally found a monster of your own level to fight.\" Maybe he\'s just jealous because he doesn\'t have one himself. (Lasts 15 minutes)"};
descriptions["11379"]={cn:"这一次，掉在你盔甲上的终于不是豆芙屎了，而是融化的巧克力。\n（持续15分钟）",en:"For once, you won\'t have Tofu droppings all down your breastplate - this time, it\'ll just be chocolate stains. \n(Lasts 15 minutes)"};
descriptions["11380"]={cn:"它梦想着成为一条真正的鱼：只溶于口，不溶于手。吃下去再说。快！\n（持续15分钟）",en:"This chocolate model dreams of being a real Snapper: It\'ll waste no time melting in your hand before slipping and slithering away forever. Eat it up, quick!\n(Lasts 15 minutes)"};
descriptions["11381"]={cn:"像巧克力一样甜，有温度也有风度。",en:"Sweet like chocolate, this hat will keep you nice and wawm."};
descriptions["11382"]={cn:"有只彩蛋兔缠在你的腰上？哇哦，放松点，现在流行这个！",en:"A Fleaster Wodent \'round your pelvis? Woah, take it easy, hot stuff!"};
descriptions["11383"]={cn:"敌人来了你真指望这件东西来保护你么？好吧，就用性感来击倒敌人吧！",en:"The pompoms don\'t really protect from enemy attack, but they\'re pretty darn sexy!"};
descriptions["11384"]={cn:"柔软的拖鞋。拿一杯可乐，在庇护袋里发发呆度过一天也挺好的。",en:"Could these slippers get any softer? Grab a mug of cocoa and prepare to feel at home in any Haven Bag."};
descriptions["11385"]={cn:"比幸运兔脚更难捡到。如果没有作用，也不要生气。实际上它确实一点用也没有！",en:"This amulet is more difficult to come by than a lucky Wodent foot. Don\'t get eggy when it doesn\'t do anything special - it is, after all, completely and utterly useless!"};
descriptions["11386"]={cn:"当然，每个人也都梦想拥有彩蛋兔指环。",en:"And, uh, who hasn\'t dreamed of having a Fleaster Wodent ring on their finger?"};
descriptions["11387"]={cn:"在肥沃的田野里种下种子后，然后马上逃命！",en:"Plant this in the earth of a fertile field and then run!"};
descriptions["11388"]={cn:"你长久以来梦想着能穿上这对护肩，不是吗？我赌10块钱一定是这样。",en:"You\'ve been looking forward to wearing these epaulettes for a long time, haven\'t you? I\'ll bet you have."};
descriptions["11389"]={cn:"如果你选择这条腰带，那么你必须得有完美的腹肌。但是别担心...你的腹肌会练得完美无瑕！",en:"With this kind of jello stuck to your stomach, your muscles will have to work twice as hard to hold it up. But don\'t worry - you\'ll end up with impeccable abs!"};
descriptions["11390"]={cn:"利矛、敌人以及疯狂的追星女孩都会被这件胸甲弹开，保护你不受伤害。",en:"Spears, enemies and manic fangirls will bounce harmlessly off this breastplate."};
descriptions["11391"]={cn:"紧紧地贴在你颈部皮肤上，摘下来的时候会很难。",en:"This necklace sticks so tightly onto the skin of your neck that you\'ll have a hard time getting it off."};
descriptions["11392"]={cn:"在用法杖痛打了某人之后，最好闭起眼睛拼命发誓你是正当防卫。酒吧会巧妙剪辑闭路电视录像，让你看起来不太像个坏蛋。",en:"After using this staff to attack someone, swear blind that it was in self-defence. The tavern can always edit its CCTV footage later to make you look like less of a baddie"};
descriptions["11393"]={cn:"如此贪婪，如此美丽。",en:"As voracious as it is beautiful."};
descriptions["11394"]={cn:"戴上之后你觉得自己的脑袋变得价值连城了。",en:"Put this crown on and you\'ll immediately feel like there\'s a price on your head."};
descriptions["11395"]={cn:"对于十二世界，这个称号比大杀器更危险。",en:"Piwis are red, Googoos are blue, show me some love and I\'ll share my Wakfu."};
descriptions["11396"]={cn:"学习使人更高，更快，更强。",en:"Learning is the key to knowledge, strength and power."};
descriptions["11397"]={cn:"坚硬的头盔，能把任何东西砸碎：无论是墙壁还是猪一样的队友。使用的时候一定要小心...",en:"This solid helmet will smash anything you want: just try it on a wall or a team-mate. Just take care when using it, will ya?"};
descriptions["11398"]={cn:"缓冲性极强，你根本分不清究竟是被绵球先锋撞了还是被绵球球撞了。",en:"These epaulettes are such good shock-absorbers that you won\'t be able to tell the difference between a hit from a War Chief and a Gobbowl Ball."};
descriptions["11403"]={cn:"秋裤洛夫斯基曾用它来整理秋裤，现在你也可以这么干。",en:"This wand will go perfectly with all the brightly-colored feathery underwear you own. Oh don\'t act all innocent!"};
descriptions["11404"]={cn:"微型匕首，一不小心就不见了。",en:"This dagger is so tiny that it\'s hard to see with the naked eye."};
descriptions["11405"]={cn:"不向任何人屈服，就算是你也不例外！",en:"This bow will bow to nobody - not even you!"};
descriptions["11406"]={cn:"永远不要信任它！",en:"This sword is not to be trusted!"};
descriptions["11407"]={cn:"大幅提高战斗技巧！底部的木质鞋钉使得靴子十分耐用。敌人会被吓得发抖！",en:"If anything will improve your butt-kicking skills it\'s these boots! The wooden spikes on the soles render them highly resistant. You stud-muffin...!"};
descriptions["11408"]={cn:"既性感又坚韧！穿上它，管他敌人多少你都不怕！",en:"It\'s sexy, solid and soooo flattering! With this wrapped around your pecs, you feel ready to smash up any number of opponents!"};
descriptions["11409"]={cn:"多汁的蟹肉，一口吃下去之后，你会流出感激的泪水。眼泪，为什么会流泪？洋葱...因为加了洋葱。",en:"This juicy meat is so sumptuous that your eyes will fill with tears of gratitude as soon as you pop it in your mouth."};
descriptions["11410"]={cn:"很久以前，人们相信智慧是金。现在，这个护符汇集了世上所有的智慧。",en:"Many moons ago, people used to say that wisdom was golden.\nNow the only wisdom left in this World is embedded deep inside this amulet."};
descriptions["11411"]={cn:"让你登高山如履平地。",en:"These boots allow plain sailing on the plains of Mount Zinit."};
descriptions["11412"]={cn:"在下雨天里也能让你保持干燥爽洁。",en:"This cloak will keep you dry on those rainy days."};
descriptions["11413"]={cn:"保护秀发免受伤害。",en:"This hat will probably give you hat hair."};
descriptions["11415"]={cn:"传说收集齐10块水行碎片，海面会分成两边，穿透敌人护甲，给敌人以致命打击。",en:"Legend has it that if you put 10 Agua Fragments together, the water will split into two and pierce enemy armor with its deadly point."};
descriptions["11416"]={cn:"现在你也可以控制海洋河流的千钧波涛了。虽然还不如艾葛贝瑞尔那般熟练，但是总比不会好。",en:"Now you too can master the water of the rivers and seas. Not as well as Aguabrial, but it\'s better than nothing."};
descriptions["11419"]={cn:"像百年化石一样柔软有弹性。",en:"These ribs are as soft and flexible as a 100-year old fossil."};
descriptions["11420"]={cn:"据说是魔法巨龙艾葛贝瑞尔制造的披风。",en:"It is said that this cape was created by a huff and a puff from Aguabrial the magic dragon."};
descriptions["11423"]={cn:"二选一：藏宝室还是怪物屋。不能都选！",en:"This ballot paper will allow you to vote for either the treasure room or the Archmonster room, but not for both at the same time! but not for both at the same time!"};
descriptions["11424"]={cn:"你选择了怪物屋！请注意你无法再选择藏宝室。",en:"This ballot paper represents your vote for the Archmonster room! Please note that you will no longer be able to vote to enter the treasure room."};
descriptions["11425"]={cn:"帽檐遮住了脸，让你得以保持神秘感。",en:"This hat hides part of your face so that you can stay in the shade. The other part of your head will obviously be in the sun... The term hot head finally makes sense!"};
descriptions["11426"]={cn:"就是它了！百分百豆芙主题的庇护袋！现在所有来拜访的女孩子都把这里当成自己的家了！",en:"With this kit, you can have a 100% Tofu-themed Haven Bag! Now all the chicks who come to visit will feel at home the moment they step in!"};
descriptions["11427"]={cn:"就让朋友们尽情嘲笑吧，你毫不在乎...没有什么比手机信号满格更重要的了。",en:"Let your friends judge you as they so wish, you don\'t care - you really rate this headwear."};
descriptions["11428"]={cn:"随时随地让所有人知道你在干什么。",en:"This belt emits regular Piwi calls to draw attention to itself. Very useful for letting absolutely everyone know exactly what you\'re doing."};
descriptions["11429"]={cn:"简单易用的项链，能帮你解答烦人的问题。不幸的是，它并不能减少你点击的次数。",en:"This simple, user-friendly necklace will help you answer all those niggly questions, but unfortunately won\'t reduce your number of hits."};
descriptions["11430"]={cn:"时尚的靴子，让你紧跟潮流，熟悉任何小道消息，八面玲珑。告别交不到朋友的时代吧！",en:"These trendy boots will keep you up to date on all the gossip and make social integration much easier. Wave goodbye to being unfriended!"};
descriptions["11431"]={cn:"事实证明你以前曾经做到过！再做一次给世界看看！",en:"It seems that you have already made it as a legendary adventurer. But can you do it a second time?"};
descriptions["11432"]={cn:"由一位专业烤串小贩设计。",en:"This helmet was designed by a professional shish-kebab arranger."};
descriptions["11433"]={cn:"这肩甲的设计初衷是让穿戴着能在水里飘浮...那么一秒钟，然后你就石沉大海了。",en:"These epaulettes are designed to make you float when you\'re in water... Unfortunately, it only works for a second before you sink like a stone."};
descriptions["11434"]={cn:"虽然又轻又薄，但是还是别再太阳底下穿...一股子鱼腥味。",en:"Although it\'s airy and light, it is best not to wear this cloak in the sun - it absolutely humdings of fish."};
descriptions["11435"]={cn:"这鞋子据说能让人铁脚水上漂，不过没人证明过...",en:"Apparently these boots enable you to walk on water, but nobody\'s proved it yet..."};
descriptions["11436"]={cn:"现在没人嘲笑你了。他们都笑瘫了。",en:"They used to laugh. Now they flee. For you... are... Zordo!"};
descriptions["11437"]={cn:"萨弗基亚人相信这根项链能带来好运，因为它在夜晚发出闪闪的红光。当然，这也意味着小偷和杀手在晚上也能毫不费力地找到你。",en:"Sufokians say that this amulet is lucky because it glows in the night. Then again, that does mean that thieves and assassins will never have trouble spotting you."};
descriptions["11438"]={cn:"必须有耐心才能收获这特殊的木材。",en:"This wood is so special that you have to learn to be patient to harvest it."};
descriptions["11439"]={cn:"不要在栗树下呆太久，否则掉下的栗子能把你砸傻。",en:"Don\'t spend too long in the plantation or you\'ll go nuts yourself."};
descriptions["11440"]={cn:"漂亮的棕栗色。",en:"This wood is a magnificent chestnutty brown color."};
descriptions["11441"]={cn:"有关于栗子，最有趣的用途就是趁着朋友不注意的时候在他床上塞上一大把。",en:"The funniest thing to do with chestnuts is to hide a large number of them in a friend\'s bed when they\'re not looking."};
descriptions["11442"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["11444"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["11445"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["11447"]={cn:"闪光蓝蓟或蓝蓟都非常有助于你的消化系统。",en:"The glistening thistle, or Glistle, will do wonders for your digestive system."};
descriptions["11448"]={cn:"就是它了！百分百疯兔主题的庇护袋！当心别被大灰狼看到！",en:"With this kit, you can have a 100% Wabbit-themed Haven Bag! Just watch out for Wabbit predators, or you\'ll find your bag and all its contents swallowed wight up!"};
descriptions["11449"]={cn:"就是它了！百分百绵球主题的庇护袋！但愿没有那股刺鼻的骚味！",en:"With this kit, you can have a 100% Gobball-themed Haven Bag! Let\'s hope that doesn\'t include the smell!"};
descriptions["11450"]={cn:"就是它了！百分百皮皮主题的庇护袋！啊，你的耳朵竖起来了！",en:"With this kit, you can have a 100% Prespic-themed Haven Bag! Ah, that\'s made your ears prick up!"};
descriptions["11451"]={cn:"这朵花虽轻，但比你预想的更加不屈不挠、坚韧不拔。",en:"This flower is so light you\'ll have a hard time believing just how rigid and resistant it is."};
descriptions["11452"]={cn:"这颗种子可以生长成漂亮的花朵。让人忍不住想亲手培育出这么漂亮的花朵。",en:"The flower that grows out of this little seed is incredibly beautiful. So beautiful, it may even help you find a place to plant your own seed."};
descriptions["11453"]={cn:"能长成新鲜的薄荷。",en:"For growing fresh mint."};
descriptions["11454"]={cn:"为所有的菜肴增添自然新鲜的口感。",en:"The Mint Leaf adds a natural freshness to all your culinary creations."};
descriptions["11455"]={cn:"蕨叶十分漂亮，经常被用来装点内衣和短裤。",en:"Fern leaves are so pretty that they\'re used for decorating underwear and wicker baskets."};
descriptions["11456"]={cn:"蕨孢子是很小的颗粒。同时又被称作伊欧普脑袋。",en:"Fern spores are very small. So small that they\'re also known as Iop brains."};
descriptions["11457"]={cn:"既恶心又粘手的鼻涕。",en:"With a name and a texture like that, one might think that this substance comes right out of a Gobball\'s nose. And yet, it doesn\'t!"};
descriptions["11458"]={cn:"无法忍受海草和海盐腐臭的气味？你该试试鼻孔藻！",en:"Can\'t stand the smell of rotting seaweed and moldy salt? You\'ll probably want to give Nostril Algae a wide birth!"};
descriptions["11459"]={cn:"柔软的蕨叶，遮挡私处的完美选择。",en:"This fern leaf is very soft, making it perfect to protect your intimate areas."};
descriptions["11461"]={cn:"把颗粒压碎，现在你多了一种上厕所的方法。",en:"Crush these grains up and they\'ll become an excellent way to go to the bathroom."};
descriptions["11462"]={cn:"燕麦秸呈白色。",en:"This straw is well known for its pale color."};
descriptions["11463"]={cn:"即便是你粗心地把种子洒落在地上，它们也会长成壮硕多汁的甜瓜。",en:"Even if you just drop these seeds carelessly on the ground, they will grow to give you big, juicy Melons."};
descriptions["11464"]={cn:"没有什么比多汁的甜瓜更能解渴的了。",en:"There\'s nothing like a juicy Melon to quench your thirst."};
descriptions["11465"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["11466"]={cn:"现在有充分时间可以在田野里播下黑麦种子，但是这并不意味着你可以无所事事，甚至闲得去打鸟。",en:"Just because you can now grow pocketfuls of rye in your fields doesn\'t mean you need to go around baking blackbirds in pies."};
descriptions["11467"]={cn:"如果你想做些坚硬的面包，那么你选对了！",en:"If you want hard, solid loaves, then this rye fiber is for you!"};
descriptions["11468"]={cn:"这种子非常适合生长在月亮岛潮湿的地下区域。",en:"This seed takes well when planted in damp Sadida Kingdom soil."};
descriptions["11469"]={cn:"斑点蘑菇被认为是完美的应急食品，尽管它的味道很糟糕。",en:"The Mottled Mushroom has long been considered the quintessential survival food, despite its rather unpleasant taste."};
descriptions["11471"]={cn:"据说这捆黄麻整夜发光，会吸引幽灵骚扰。",en:"People say that this Jute shines all night long and attracts Ghostofs."};
descriptions["11472"]={cn:"手工磨制。",en:"Rice, rice, baby. Vanilla."};
descriptions["11473"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["11474"]={cn:"现在种下它，一整年都不缺稻米。",en:"Plant this now and you\'ll have enough Vanilla Rice to last you all year round."};
descriptions["11475"]={cn:"大千世界里的一只小小哞崽。你一整天盯着它发呆，或者玩弄它的尾巴。",en:"This little Moogrroon is a simple creature in a big, scary world. You could gaze at its bemused expression and constantly swishing tail for hours!"};
descriptions["11476"]={cn:"请好好照看这只鸵鸟。它脸皮很厚的，你逃跑的时候它比你跑得还快，小心别被它绊倒了。",en:"Take good care of this Strich. It is audacious and will follow you whilst you run for your life! Just go careful not to break your ankle if it trips you up."};
descriptions["11477"]={cn:"这只螃蟹和你在一起的时候显得很自在，但是小心点...他是个隐士。",en:"This Cwab will feel at home with you, but be careful - he\'s a bit of a hermit."};
descriptions["11478"]={cn:"你是不是觉得如果铁矿长得跟水晶一样，就不能像往常一样粗暴的加工了呢？那你就错了！",en:"You certainly wouldn\'t expect ore to gain a crystalline look by treating it with an iron fist, but this proves otherwise!"};
descriptions["11479"]={cn:"煤是生火的利器。布拉克玛的孩子们每年圣诞节在袜子里找到这些煤矿的时候都会激动得发抖。",en:"Carbon is great for starting fires. That\'s why Brakmarian children are so thrilled to receive a lump of it in their stockings each year."};
descriptions["11480"]={cn:"与夜色融为一体的矿石，闪耀着淡淡的蓝色。",en:"The darker it is, the shadier this Shadowy Cobalt looks."};
descriptions["11481"]={cn:"这东西是金子哦...骑士们都相信的！",en:"The tradition is to try to make a Iop believe that a Bronze Nugget is actually a golden nugget... and it works!"};
descriptions["11482"]={cn:"别用一块燧石去摩擦另一块燧石，很多人就是这样玩火死的。",en:"Careful you don\'t rub two shards of flint together too hard; dangerous things have been discovered that way."};
descriptions["11483"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["11484"]={cn:"高密度金属，经常被用于珠宝。",en:"This dense metal is often used to make jewelry."};
descriptions["11485"]={cn:"抗腐蚀抗污浊。现在你知道为什么陪葬的泪石武器不太容易生锈了吧。",en:"This hard metal is resistant to corrosion and tarnish, which is why Grievous Kroomium weapons found buried next to fallen soldiers are still in such good nick."};
descriptions["11486"]={cn:"传说以前的冒险者会用笑颜石制成的武器和他们心爱的人一同下葬，这样在冥界就能安然无恙。",en:"According to an old story, adventurers used to bury weapons forged with this Kroomium into tombs alongside their loved ones, so they\'d be able to defend themselves in the world of the dead."};
descriptions["11487"]={cn:"找到这种矿石的最简单方法就是跟随矿道另一端的亮光。",en:"If you\'re having trouble mining this ore just look for the light at the end of the tunnel."};
descriptions["11489"]={cn:"只有在特别的水域才能找到这种鲟鱼。",en:"This Sturgeon can only be found in unusual waters."};
descriptions["11490"]={cn:"白色的银鲈鱼，肉质粉嫩。在爱鱼者中广受欢迎。",en:"White Perch is a white fish, obviously, with a floury sort of texture. A big hit with fish fans."};
descriptions["11491"]={cn:"这种龙鲤的鳞片闪闪发亮，时不时在空中映射出三重彩虹。",en:"This Dragocarp\'s scales are so shiny that they sometimes send a triple rainbow skittering all across the sky."};
