descriptions["11544"]={cn:"轻轻一触，就会化为尘埃。",en:"This petal will disintegrate into dust at the slightest touch."};
descriptions["11545"]={cn:"十分脆弱的树枝，也是最轻的树枝。",en:"This brittle branch is very fragile, but it\'s also one of the lightest branches ever."};
descriptions["11546"]={cn:"这件头饰的前端是用来反射阳光照瞎敌人眼睛的，所以夏天真的很管用，冬天么...不说了。",en:"Sunlight reflects off the front of this tiara to blind enemies and leave them helpless. Works like a charm in the summer, but winter\'s another story."};
descriptions["11547"]={cn:"如果獠牙看上去很好斗，这很容易理解，它们天生就这样。",en:"Don\'t be annoyed if this tusk acts all defensive. It\'s just in its nature."};
descriptions["11548"]={cn:"点击两下来把整组古代资源转换成新的资源。古代资源需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["11549"]={cn:"取自红酒咕哩的胃部，散发着酒香。可从咕哩泥塘里面，饿肚子的宝箱怪取得。",en:"This bile came straight from Boarnigen\'s stomach, but it still tastes relatively fresh and fruity. This item can be obtained thanks to the Famished Mimik in the Blibli Dungeon."};
descriptions["11550"]={cn:"果肉饱满的橘子。",en:"An orange filled with juicy red pulp."};
descriptions["11551"]={cn:"据说这个独角仙护符能让任何人变得更聪明...所以我们决定让你试试！",en:"They say that this Scara necklace can make absolutely anyone intelligent... so we decided to test it on you!"};
descriptions["11554"]={cn:"不仅仅是陈年老便。富含大量黄金，让你分不清究竟该收藏还是丢弃。",en:"This is not just any old dung. This dung contains copious amounts of gold, which makes you wonder whether you should like or lump it."};
descriptions["11555"]={cn:"点击两下来把整组古代资源转换成新的资源。古代资源需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["11556"]={cn:"粘牙的奶糖，新鲜出炉，熔岩独角仙刚拉的。",en:"A mouth-gluing piece of fudge, fresh from the rear end of a Melty Scaramel."};
descriptions["11557"]={cn:"好吃的巧克力糖角，让你的每一天都像星期天！",en:"This chocolate horn tastes so good that every day feels like the weekend!"};
descriptions["11558"]={cn:"和刀锋一样锐利的薄片，要小心问你借的人。",en:"This foil is as sharp as a razor, so be careful who you lend it to."};
descriptions["11559"]={cn:"即便被扯下来，仍然酷劲十足。",en:"Even all ripped up, this dorsal fin looks way cool."};
descriptions["11560"]={cn:"点击两下来把整组古代资源转换成新的资源。古代资源需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["11561"]={cn:"异常难闻，据说会带来厄运。所以...捡起来的家伙，恭喜你！",en:"This beak smells, it\'s clammy to the touch and it\'s said to bring bad luck. So... congrats on picking it up!"};
descriptions["11562"]={cn:"鱼怪们眼神不好，不知道这是啥颜色！",en:"Snappy has terrible aim, just look what he\'s reeled in!"};
descriptions["11563"]={cn:"既然你可以用这个护符诅咒敌人，为什么还要拼命地在战场上奔波呢？",en:"Why waste your time glowering across the battlefield at your enemy when you can just curse them using this amulet?"};
descriptions["11564"]={cn:"点击两下来把旧物品转换成相同类型的新物品。",en:"Double-click to transform your old item into a new one of the same type."};
descriptions["11565"]={cn:"点击两下来把旧物品转换成相同类型的新物品。",en:"Double-click to transform your old item into a new one of the same type."};
descriptions["11566"]={cn:"点击两下来把旧物品转换成相同类型的新物品。",en:"Double-click to transform your old item into a new one of the same type."};
descriptions["11567"]={cn:"点击两下来把旧物品转换成相同类型的新物品。",en:"Double-click to transform your old item into a new one of the same type."};
descriptions["11568"]={cn:"鲨鱼的利齿能穿透任何种类的木材。带上它，你将成为优秀的伐木工斗士！",en:"Shark teeth are well-known for being able to saw through all types of wood. With this sword, you\'ll be a fighter-slash-lumberjack par excellence!"};
descriptions["11569"]={cn:"只要摆放的位置正确，就能喷射出跨越天际的彩虹。",en:"Position this shard correctly to create a double rainbow, all the way across the sky."};
descriptions["11570"]={cn:"专为健康的口腔提供。",en:"For healthy jaws."};
descriptions["11571"]={cn:"调查结果正在核实中，我们需要知道这血是鲨鱼的还是受害者身上的。",en:"Tests are underway to investigate whether this blood came from a Selachii or from one of its victims."};
descriptions["11572"]={cn:"别费劲了，怎么揪都揪不掉的。",en:"Whatever you chuck it at, there it will stay."};
descriptions["11573"]={cn:"我有个朋友曾经戴过同一款式的帽子。有一天，他勇敢地向一群呆呱挑战。从那以后，我再也没有听到过他的消息...",en:"I had a friend who used to wear a hat like this all the time. But one day, he ventured into an Oafish Toad colony, and was never heard from again..."};
descriptions["11576"]={cn:"因为护符上的蚊眼，使你腹背受敌。",en:"Thanks to the Moskito eye adorning this amulet, you can anticipate oncoming danger from all four directions."};
descriptions["11577"]={cn:"戴上帽子，自我感觉变成了执政官。但是你实际上只是个笨蛋。",en:"You think you look fit to be a Governor in the Chafer King\'s hat, but you actually just look like a dork."};
descriptions["11578"]={cn:"骸骨之王只在特殊场合才穿上这件披风。事实上，他是穿着这件披风被干掉的。",en:"The Chafer King only wears this cloak for special occasions. As a matter of fact, it just so happened that he was wearing it the day he was killed."};
descriptions["11579"]={cn:"依附着骸骨之王的灵魂。睡觉的时候别戴着，否则鼻子会莫名抽搐。",en:"This amulet was bewitched by the spirit of the Chafer King. Unless you want it to make your nose twitch uncontrollably, it\'s best not to wear it in bed."};
descriptions["11580"]={cn:"鲨鱼的利齿能穿透任何种类的木材。带上它，你将成为优秀的伐木工斗士！",en:"Shark teeth are well-known for being able to saw through all types of wood. With this sword, you\'ll be a fighter-slash-lumberjack par excellence!"};
descriptions["11581"]={cn:"鲨鱼的利齿能穿透任何种类的木材。带上它，你将成为优秀的伐木工斗士！",en:"Shark teeth are well-known for being able to saw through all types of wood. With this sword, you\'ll be a fighter-slash-lumberjack par excellence!"};
descriptions["11582"]={cn:"鲨鱼的利齿能穿透任何种类的木材。带上它，你将成为优秀的伐木工斗士！",en:"Shark teeth are well-known for being able to saw through all types of wood. With this sword, you\'ll be a fighter-slash-lumberjack par excellence!"};
descriptions["11583"]={cn:"这对护肩的起源是一个黑暗、深邃的秘密。我们只知道它们有着强大的力量。",en:"The origin of these epaulettes is a dark, deep secret. All that is known is that they have great powers."};
descriptions["11584"]={cn:"设计欠佳，太紧了点。魁梧的骑士们穿着会有点小麻烦。对于刺客来说却很贴身。",en:"Too tight and badly-designed, the Chafer King\'s belt has some trouble adapting to Iop use. For Srams, however, it should be a perfect fit."};
descriptions["11585"]={cn:"传说很久很久以前，一位名叫亚瑟的年轻农夫发现了这柄祖传的宝剑，下面没有了...",en:"This sword was discovered by a young peasant called Arthur. Nobody knows what happened next."};
descriptions["11586"]={cn:"点击两下来把整组古代资源转换成新的资源。古代资源需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["11587"]={cn:"多多跪拜，你就明白这颗牙齿的用途了。",en:"Learn to love and respect this resource and its multiple uses will become apparent."};
descriptions["11588"]={cn:"坚硬的白骨胸甲，能防止小矮人攻击你的头。",en:"A tough little breastplate that will put an end to short people trying to headbutt you."};
descriptions["11590"]={cn:"看，内壁上有字！等等，只是一点灰尘。",en:"Look! There\'s an inscription! Oh wait, it\'s just a bit of dirt."};
descriptions["11591"]={cn:"不仅造型拉风，还能替你抵挡萨弗基亚的烈日。",en:"In addition to being really cool, this superb hat will protect you from the Sufokian sun."};
descriptions["11592"]={cn:"不同于巨魔大棒能一击置人于死地，它更善于一刀刀杀伤敌人。",en:"This little number won\'t hurt as much as a Trool bludgeon, but it\'s a much more subtle, tasteful means of attack."};
descriptions["11593"]={cn:"在阳光下暴晒了很久，导致它看上去憔悴不堪。",en:"This Palm Tree Leaf has been in the sun too long, which explains its rather battered appearance."};
descriptions["11594"]={cn:"你需要再把腰带系紧一点儿。它的前主人太胖了。",en:"Go ahead and tighten this belt a few notches. The previous owner was a bit too roly-poly."};
descriptions["11595"]={cn:"缺乏实用性，但是在沙滩上没有比穿凉爽的护胫更合适的了。",en:"These boots appear to lack practicality, but can you imagine anything more comfortable for wearing on the beach? These boots appear to lack practicality, but can you imagine anything more comfortable for wearing on the beach?"};
descriptions["11596"]={cn:"雨林深处，椰茎独处。石榴芒果，充饥果腹。极品指环，只能轻拂。呜呼，呜呼，只能轻拂。",en:"Way down deep in the middle of the jungle, a Kokoko took this ring, a guava and a mango. Kokobungo, Kokobungo, they wear it in the jungle..."};
descriptions["11597"]={cn:"有些人能熟练地用这种铲子摘椰子，而大部分人只会用它拌泥团。",en:"Some people are skillful enough to use this shovel to harvest Kokonuts. Most of them just use it to make mud pies though."};
