descriptions["11599"]={cn:"你的战利品是椰子味的胡须。",en:"A Kokonut-flavored beard that you picked up from one of your conquests."};
descriptions["11600"]={cn:"海滩上晒日光浴的最佳选择。这条腰带在各种战斗中给与你强有力的支持。",en:"Highly practical for sunbathing on the beach, this belt offers unbeatable support in stormy battles."};
descriptions["11601"]={cn:"某张藏宝图的残片。\n不幸的是，星期一的那一页不见了。",en:"These cards are actually pieces of a treasure map. Unfortunately, Monday\'s page is missing."};
