descriptions["11666"]={cn:"凝视着卷轴，能帮助你整理思绪。",en:"Just gazing at this sculpture for a while will help you get all your thoughts in alphabetical order."};
descriptions["11667"]={cn:"不仅能用来招揽盟友，战斗中也很有用。",en:"Whip out this tough, sturdy bone to impress your allies. It\'s pretty useful in combat too."};
descriptions["11668"]={cn:"让你忘却烦恼纷争，现代生活必须。",en:"This sculpture will allow you to forget about your worries and your strife, which are of course the bare necessities in life."};
descriptions["11669"]={cn:"一张标准的桌子，用来吃饭或者放东西都可以。",en:"This table is pretty standard. Useful for eating off or putting things on top of."};
descriptions["11670"]={cn:"猫头鹰博闻强识，这是众所周知的事实。那他们知道自己和喵喵有什么亲戚关系吗？",en:"It\'s a well-known fact: owls know everything. It\'s a real hoot to be able to know everything all of a sudden!"};
descriptions["11671"]={cn:"智者有言，猫头鹰长得像喵喵...",en:"Wise men say only owls rush in..."};
descriptions["11672"]={cn:"别只把种子放桌子上...拿去播种！俗话说懒惰是万恶之源。",en:"Don\'t let this table go to seed - get planting! After all, idleness is the root of all evil."};
descriptions["11673"]={cn:"不仅能用来招揽盟友，战斗中也很有用。",en:"Whip out this tough, sturdy bone to impress your allies. It\'s pretty useful in combat too."};
