descriptions["11677"]={cn:"这张桌子上刻了一幅绵球的解剖图，能让你正确的知道去哪里采集它们的种子。",en:"This table has a diagram of a Gobball\'s anatomy on top, just in case you\'re having trouble guessing where exactly to sow its seed."};
descriptions["11678"]={cn:"别大惊小怪的，这张桌子刚刚被人屠杀了。怎么说呢，你都用它吃饭了，它怎么就不能被人杀呢？",en:"It\'s no surprise that this table is absolutely butchered, but hey, one man\'s poison is another man\'s meat."};
descriptions["11679"]={cn:"世代草药师传承至今，百分百纯草药制成。请务必温柔对待，每天伴着音乐好好擦拭它。",en:"Passed down from herbalist to herbalist for generations, this table is absolutely dill - you\'re going to lovage it! Sage thyme by parsley cleaning it every day and take good care of it."};
descriptions["11680"]={cn:"想跟地穴兽交朋友？最好的方法是用一桌过期的好东西来招待它们。",en:"There\'s no better way to make friends with your Drhellers than by holding a good old-fashioned beanfeast."};
descriptions["11681"]={cn:"这张桌子一股鱼腥味。没办法，跟渔夫有关的东西都这个味道。",en:"Something may have smelt fishy when you got this table but don\'t you know you must lose a fly to catch a trout?"};
descriptions["11682"]={cn:"你总是以没有地方施展厨艺为借口拒绝下厨。这张小桌子让你完全没借口了！",en:"You always say you can\'t cook because you don\'t have the space. This handy little table will put an end to that!"};
descriptions["11683"]={cn:"黑白相间的花纹，正是时下流行的配色...",en:"Apparently black and white is all the rage at the moment..."};
descriptions["11684"]={cn:"你知道那个有名的龙鸟高手埃姆斯塔丹吗，他其实是个药剂师，弄了什么药吃所以才跑这么快的。",en:"Famous apothecary Amstadamus discourages mixing your medicines directly below your nose, unless of course you want to end up light-headed."};
descriptions["11685"]={cn:"你用冬天铸造的卡玛买的吗？好冷，坐上去别冻着屁股了。",en:"This table is brrrrrrilliant. Alright, you paid cold, hard cash for it and now that\'s frozen in your memory, but don\'t let it snow you under, just chill out."};
descriptions["11686"]={cn:"上面放了个头骨模型，显出一股学者的气息。",en:"Wear your fingers to the bone with this skull topped table."};
descriptions["11687"]={cn:"用这张桌子做出来的面包，其松软程度取决于你臀部的质地。",en:"Don\'t loaf around when using this table, you worked your buns off to get it."};
descriptions["11688"]={cn:"花言巧语都是虚的，仔细从字里行间中探索它的言外之意吧。用功读书，你能亲眼见证自己的未来。",en:"Fine words punish no parsnips, but if you read between the lines you\'ll see that the writing is not actually on the wall just yet. Hit the books and your future will be spelt out before your very eyes."};
descriptions["11689"]={cn:"这张桌子是用来收藏的，名副其实，千真万确。",en:"This table is a real collector\'s item."};
descriptions["11690"]={cn:"你从霓家买来的时候应该附送了几张说明书吧，动起手来，照着说明来拼装吧。",en:"Wholeseller IDEA deliver this table with instructions so you\'ll know how to assemble it."};
descriptions["11691"]={cn:"手掌交叉放在这张桌子上，在点缀些银饰，它就能成为你庇护袋里的明珠。",en:"Cross your palm with silver on this table enough and it will become the jewel in your crown."};
descriptions["11692"]={cn:"传说世界上的炼金术士们都是同一个化学老师教的。",en:"Rumor has it that all the World\'s alchemists have entered into a secret chemical brotherhood."};
descriptions["11693"]={cn:"拥有这张桌子不代表你拥有了木材，继续工作吧...钱不是长在树上的。",en:"Just because you have this workbench doesn\'t mean you\'re out of the woods just yet. Keep on plying - money doesn\'t grow on trees."};
descriptions["11694"]={cn:"你得往下挖很深才能弄到这张桌子，毕竟跟矿有关的东西都得靠挖才能弄到。",en:"You may have had to dig deep to get this table but at least now you can say, \"It\'s mine\" and truly mean it."};
descriptions["11695"]={cn:"可爱得让你想一口吃下去！显然，你不会真的这么做。吞咽危险。",en:"He\'s so cute you could eat him wight up! Obviously, you won\'t actually do that, as it would be terribly dangerous."};
descriptions["11696"]={cn:"它不会飞。所以不要再把它丢来丢去了。",en:"Nope, it doesn\'t fly, so stop flinging it across your Haven Bag like a loon."};
descriptions["11697"]={cn:"跟真的野猪一样！更软更漂亮，更...轻。",en:"Just like the real thing! But softer, nicer and much, much lighter."};
descriptions["11698"]={cn:"你才是逗逗，你全家都是逗逗。",en:"This Tofu has really seen life, man."};
descriptions["11699"]={cn:"十二世界中最早被创造出来的东西之一。阿玛克纳普通人家的客厅里经常可以见到。各地收藏家必备！",en:"This soft toy was one of the first to be made in the World of Twelve, and takes pride of place in many Amaknian living rooms. A must-have for collectors everywhere!"};
descriptions["11700"]={cn:"给另一半的完美礼物！最好每年拿到的都不一样，否则珍贵度就降低了。",en:"The perfect gift for your other half! Just make sure you don\'t get the same one every year, the novelty wears off."};
descriptions["11701"]={cn:"不一定是你想的那种尖刺，但是你不得不承认它的形状优美。",en:"It might not be the kind of stake you were hoping for, but you have to admit it\'s a very graceful shape."};
