descriptions["11706"]={cn:"泰坦巨人们经常举行庆典来膜拜他们的国王。这就是他们当时戴的皇冠。",en:"The titans used to hold festivals in Javian to worship their kings. This is the kind of hat they wore."};
descriptions["11707"]={cn:"可以用来兑换糖果。去阿斯图布的酒窖里一探究竟吧！",en:"A token which will win you some candy, of course! Get down to the inn in Astrub to find out more!"};
descriptions["11708"]={cn:"很经典啊，没啥特色。",en:"A simple dresser with an unerring desire to hold your things."};
descriptions["11709"]={cn:"裁缝、士兵、间谍...",en:"Soldier Spy."};
descriptions["11710"]={cn:"你肯定很奇怪，为什么猫头鹰需要床头柜。管它那么多...现在是你的了！",en:"You might ask yourself why on earth an owl would need a dresser. Who cares... it\'s yours now!"};
descriptions["11711"]={cn:"你需要像动物一样低吼着跳一段奇怪的舞蹈才能打开这个柜子。",en:"To open this dresser you will need to perform a secret dance whilst grunting like an animal."};
descriptions["11712"]={cn:"很抱歉，这个柜子上全是刺，一枝玫瑰也没有。从好的方面来讲，不怕被偷。",en:"Unfortunately this thorny dresser has no rose. On the plus side, potential thieves will have a prickly time trying to steal your belongings."};
descriptions["11713"]={cn:"根据梳妆台上散发出的恶臭来看，肯定有兽人在里面躲藏了很久。",en:"Given the stench that emanates from this dresser, a Bwork must have been closed inside for some time."};
descriptions["11714"]={cn:"放心，那上面并不是真的喵喵。幸运猫设计师这么做的原因是希望能够提前吓住小偷。",en:"Don\'t worry, that\'s not a real Bow Meow on the top. The Ecaflip that designed this dresser thought it might deter theives."};
descriptions["11715"]={cn:"能放下你所有的残羹剩饭以及花园残渣，并将其转化为健康、肥沃的土壤。最重要的是，它很便宜。",en:"This dresser will take all of your old food and garden waste and turn it into healthy, rich soil. It\'s also dirt cheap. Compost Dresser"};
descriptions["11716"]={cn:"醒来映入眼帘的第一件东西，很漂亮的床头柜。",en:"A dresser that always looks its best, even first thing in the morning."};
descriptions["11717"]={cn:"有两块木板这么厚。",en:"This dresser is as thick as two short planks."};
descriptions["11718"]={cn:"真正的收藏品。为最勇敢的（好吧，最有钱的）英雄倾力打造。",en:"A real collection piece, this dresser was made for the finest (well, the richest) heros."};
descriptions["11719"]={cn:"柜子上有个游戏桌。棒极了！",en:"This dresser has a built-in board game on the top. Fantastico!"};
descriptions["11720"]={cn:"不要被夜晚听到阴森可怕的声音吓到了。哦，显然你已经适应了...",en:"Once you\'ve installed this piece of furniture, you\'ll start hearing bone-scraping sounds during the night. Apparently you get used to it..."};
descriptions["11721"]={cn:"手绘的床头柜，必须放置于温暖干燥处，否则会变得丑陋不堪。",en:"This hand-painted dresser needs to be kept in a warm, dry place otherwise it\'ll get shivery timbers."};
descriptions["11722"]={cn:"我们不知道奥古之乱要持续多久，所以多留一点粮食总是好的。",en:"We don\'t know how long Ogrest\'s Chaos will last so it\'s always a good idea to set rations aside."};
descriptions["11723"]={cn:"妻子总是告诉我说：亲爱的，一定要把盘子放在碗下面哦！\n她现在是我前妻。",en:"My wife always used to say to me, \"Sweety, make sure you put the plates under the bowls!\" She is now my ex-wife."};
descriptions["11724"]={cn:"克伯希先生是命运派公会在阿斯图布的首领。他亲手只做了这只梳妆台。奇怪的是，有一股阴雨天的绵球骚味。",en:"This magnificent masterpiece was hand sculpted by Michelangecrow, head of the Destiny guild in Astrub. Strangely enough, it only smells of Gobball on rainy days."};
descriptions["11725"]={cn:"柜面是用胡萝卜做的。",en:"This dresser has a Cawwot top. Wabbit Dresser"};
descriptions["11726"]={cn:"用于储存你的所有草药。你的朋友们嫉妒得发疯了。",en:"This dresser is just perfect for storing all your medicinal plant mixes. Your friends will be green with envy."};
descriptions["11727"]={cn:"这柜子同时也是一个住所，但是没人知道谁住在里面。有人说那是条黑暗龟鱼，也有人说是一匹年老的变异海马。",en:"This dresser is also a home, but nobody knows who lives inside. Some say it\'s a Dark Chefish, others say it\'s an old, mutated Chehorse."};
