descriptions["11735"]={cn:"不论你是汉子还是妹子，老鼠还是老虎，你都应当自豪地戴着这顶沙皇后冠...算了还是藏在包里吧...",en:"Whether you\'re man or mouse, woman or wolf, you should wear this Czarina on your head proudly... or maybe just hide it in your bag..."};
