descriptions["11747"]={cn:"这些半透明的甲虫翅膀在白天闪耀着柔和的光芒，要小心对待他们，因为它们可能会反抗哟。",en:"These translucent Scaraleaf wings sparkle gently in daylight. Careful with them though, as they\'re not particularly resistant."};
descriptions["11748"]={cn:"假如你还没意识到这张桌子有多危险，至少保持有一个治愈者跟在你身边，除非你想像波斯猴子一样死去。",en:"In case you hadn\'t realized, this table is pretty dangerous. Keep an Eniripsa on hand as a guinea-pig unless you want to end up spiked to death like the Prince of Persha."};
descriptions["11749"]={cn:"很实用的桌子，上面装配了一整套烧烤用具。你能用它来烤整只绵球或者制作烟熏鸵鸟火腿。不过话说回来，工具再好手艺不强也没用...",en:"This practical table, equipped with its own grill, has the capacity to barbecue Gobball legs to perfection and smoke Strich ham to a T. Remember, poor craftsmen always blame their tools..."};
descriptions["11750"]={cn:"整天工作没有娱乐时间，孩子们都会变迟钝的。",en:"Because all work and no play makes you a dull boy."};
descriptions["11751"]={cn:"伙计们，过来看看这个箱子里可以塞多少个线团。当然，它也可以被用作喵喵的游乐场！",en:"Fellow tailors, gather round to see just how many ribbons this chest can hold. It also makes a great play-pen for your Bow Meow!"};
descriptions["11752"]={cn:"这只褪色的柜子是园艺师的梦想。排列整齐，你再也不用翻箱倒柜地找种子了！",en:"This faded cupboard is a gardener\'s dream. It\'s so well organized that you\'ll never waste time rooting around for the right pack of seeds again!"};
descriptions["11753"]={cn:"这些半透明的甲虫翅膀在白天闪耀着柔和的光芒，要小心对待他们，因为它们可能会反抗哟。",en:"These translucent Scaraleaf wings sparkle gently in daylight. Careful with them though, as they\'re not particularly resistant."};
