descriptions["11757"]={cn:"就像星魔一样，这只柜子的容量是无限的。不幸的是，它也有不断往外吐东西的习惯。你得小心了！",en:"Just like a Gobgob, this cupboard keeps on revealing new storage space. Unfortunately, it also has a habit of spitting its contents out from time to time. You\'ve been warned!"};
descriptions["11758"]={cn:"挠挠它，它也许会愿意自动打开抽屉！",en:"Tickle this cupboard in the right spot and it might just open its drawers!"};
descriptions["11759"]={cn:"吱吱发响，能容纳你的扫帚、海绵、掸子以及抹布。",en:"A squeaky clean cupboard with room for your brooms as well as all your sponges, dusters and dishcloths."};
descriptions["11760"]={cn:"是时间变慢了还是你的新鞋让你速度太慢？",en:"Has time slowed down or is it just those funny new shoes of yours?"};
descriptions["11761"]={cn:"一旦你安装了这只橱柜，夜晚你会听到争吵声。别怕，你会习惯的。",en:"Once you\'ve installed this piece of furniture, you\'ll start hearing bone-scraping sounds during the night. Don\'t sweat it, though, you\'ll get used to it."};
descriptions["11762"]={cn:"如果你在50岁前仍然没有一个像样的柜子，我替你害羞。",en:"If you don\'t have a Prestigious Cupboard by the time you\'re 50, you\'ve failed at life."};
descriptions["11763"]={cn:"你以为无底橱将指引你进入拉尼亚的世界，实际上你只是在庇护袋里闹着玩。",en:"You hoped this cupboard would lead you back to the secret world of Narania, but it actually just leads back to your Haven Bag."};
descriptions["11764"]={cn:"哈巴德奶奶的柜子始终空无一物，这样别人就不会去她家里翻箱倒柜了。当心，你永远不知道她藏了些什么东西！",en:"Grandma Hubbard used to say that her cupboard was bare so that people wouldn\'t go rifling through her things. Careful, you never know what she might have hidden in there!"};
descriptions["11765"]={cn:"是时间变慢了还是你的新鞋让你速度太慢？",en:"Has time slowed down or is it just those funny new shoes of yours?"};
