descriptions["11768"]={cn:"穿上这双鞋子，你走路的姿势就会变得像夸夸。那么你会不会叫起来像夸夸或者像夸夸一样飞呢？当然不会，你穿的是鹅掌！",en:"With these shoes you will definitely look like a duck and walk like a duck. The question is will you quack like a duck and fly like a duck...? Course you won\'t, they\'re Goose Feet!"};
descriptions["11769"]={cn:"一件精美的复制品，原物在奥古之乱时失踪了。",en:"A sumptuous replica of a Mornande Wardrobe from the Koalak tribes, who disappeared after Ogrest\'s Chaos."};
