descriptions["11793"]={cn:"即便是最坚固的障碍也不能承受它的轰炸！用这个炸弹摧毁图铎石。",en:"Even the toughest blocks will have a hard time standing up to it! \nUse this bomb to destroy Tuhard blocks."};
descriptions["11794"]={cn:"这个帽子会使你的声音变成难以入耳的吱吱声。",en:"This hat will make your voice even more squeaky and unbearable than usual."};
descriptions["11795"]={cn:"一股老鼠味？哦...那只是你的戒指。",en:"Warning! Oops, too late..."};
descriptions["11796"]={cn:"魔杖的制造者只有四根手指。",en:"Whoever made this wand only had four fingers."};
descriptions["11797"]={cn:"全世界的幸运猫都在追着你跑。",en:"The smell of this cape will have all the Ecaflips in the territory hot on your tail."};
descriptions["11798"]={cn:"太小了，只能带在你的脚踝上。放心，不是你太胖。",en:"This belt isn\'t adjustable, and it\'s so slimy that it\'s likely to end up around your ankles."};
descriptions["11799"]={cn:"天生反骨，不断诱惑你的朋友背叛你。",en:"This cloak is so atrocious that your allies and enemies will revolt with revoltedness."};
descriptions["11800"]={cn:"总有苍蝇围着你飞。它们本来是围着便便飞的，吃饭的时候别说这么恶心的事...",en:"These epaulettes will have the flies in your vicinity dropping like, well, flies."};
