descriptions["11807"]={cn:"感谢上帝你总算可以把这条腰带隐藏在衣服下面了。千万不要露出来，会吓到小朋友的！",en:"Thank god you can hide this belt under your clothes. Just hope it doesn\'t rear its ugly head - now that wouldn\'t be a sight for sore eyes!"};
