descriptions["11812"]={cn:"这枚戒指和真正的噬影之牙一样，整天唠唠叨叨...虽然有时她的想法还不错，但是粉色十分讨人厌！",en:"You might find this ring quite annoying and rude, just like the real Shadofang...! If the thought of her wasn\'t enough to offend, the shade of pink certainly is!"};
