descriptions["11815"]={cn:"这枚戒指和真正的噬影之牙一样，整天唠唠叨叨...虽然有时她的想法还不错，但是粉色十分讨人厌！",en:"You might find this ring quite annoying and rude, just like the real Shadofang...! If the thought of her wasn\'t enough to offend, the shade of pink certainly is!"};
descriptions["11816"]={cn:"这顶帽子不断吸引着鸟儿，同时也让漂亮姑娘们对你敬而远之。",en:"This hat is a bird magnet. Believe me, you look very powerful when a Googoo decides to perch on your head. However, it might act as more of a repellent for the ladies when a Lilpiwi decides to do the same..."};
descriptions["11817"]={cn:"终于有了一件本来就很脏的衬衣，再也不用担心变得更脏了。你根本不需要去洗它。就像一块陈年奶酪，会随着时间沉淀越来越诱人，甚至连气味也是。",en:"Finally a naturally dirty shirt that you\'re not afraid of getting grubby. You don\'t even have to wash it. Like good cheese, it gets better with time, smell included."};
descriptions["11818"]={cn:"多功能的披风，如果觉得穿着不舒服还可以当船帆、吊床或者围兜使用。",en:"This multifunctional cloak can also be used as a sail, a hammock or even a bib, in case you feel a little bit queasy."};
descriptions["11819"]={cn:"穿起来显得精神极了！第一眼看上去能让人在甲板上如履平地，但是实际上只会让你双脚肿胀。起码当你被扔进海里喂鱼的时候还能当救生圈用...",en:"Buckle up for some hale and hearty fun! These boots might look like they\'ll give you sea legs but they\'ll actually just make your feet bulge. At least when you get thrown overboard you can use them to float... Just swell, oooh arr!"};
descriptions["11820"]={cn:"由盗贼约翰·水银设计，他独创的裁缝手艺至今仍然是个秘密。现在的年轻人只会到处抄袭现成的。",en:"This cape was designed by Rogue John Quicksilver, who did well to make sure his secret tailoring pattern remained secret. The youth of today often resort to stealing just to get a replica."};
descriptions["11821"]={cn:"穿起来显得精神极了！第一眼看上去能让人在甲板上如履平地，但是实际上只会让你双脚肿胀。起码当你被扔进海里喂鱼的时候还能当救生圈用...",en:"Buckle up for some hale and hearty fun! These boots might look like they\'ll give you sea legs but they\'ll actually just make your feet bulge. At least when you get thrown overboard you can use them to float... Just swell, oooh arr!"};
descriptions["11822"]={cn:"哦，亲爱的，你穿这条裙子漂亮极了！",en:"Yee, me hearty, be reelin\' in all the hearties with this fine, fine garrrment."};
descriptions["11823"]={cn:"蕾丝花边和缎带装饰的帽子。戴上这顶帽子你看起来棒极了。只是你不得不到处逃命。",en:"Decorated with lace and ribbon, with this hat you can be sure you\'ll stay looking good, despite being absolutely filthy from all that running around."};
descriptions["11843"]={cn:"丝线是物品制作中的理想原料。通过10级草药制作，可用于21-35级装备等用品制作。",en:"Rudimentary string for all apprentice tailors."};
descriptions["11844"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["11845"]={cn:"阿玛克纳土匪是大土匪家族中最活跃的一派，这张面具是他们狡猾的证明。",en:"The Amakna Riktus are the most robust of the widespread Riktus family and this breastplate makes that very clear."};
descriptions["11846"]={cn:"邦塔土匪是大土匪家族中最顽固的一派，这张面具也显示出了正统坚固的风格。",en:"The Bonta Riktus are as hard as nails and the most resistant of the widespread Riktus family. This breastplate follows suit."};
descriptions["11847"]={cn:"布拉克玛土匪以他们超人的力量闻名于世，所以不要低估这张面具能造成的伤害。",en:"The Brakmar Riktus are known for their super-human force, so don\'t underestimate the damage that this breastplate can inflict."};
descriptions["11848"]={cn:"萨弗基亚土匪以打游击闻名，这并不意味着他们害怕正面进攻！",en:"The Sufokia Riktus are primarily renowned for their robbing and running, but they\'re not afraid of attacking if they have to!"};
descriptions["11849"]={cn:"阿玛克纳土匪是大土匪家族中最活跃的一派，这对护肩是他们狡猾的证明。",en:"The Amakna Riktus are the most robust of the widespread Riktus family and this breastplate makes that very clear."};
descriptions["11850"]={cn:"邦塔土匪是大土匪家族中最顽固的一派，这对护肩也显示出了正统坚固的风格。",en:"The Bonta Riktus are as hard as nails and the most resistant of the widespread Riktus family. This breastplate follows suit."};
