descriptions["11857"]={cn:"阿玛克纳土匪是大土匪家族中最活跃的一派，这件胸甲是他们狡猾的证明。",en:"The Amakna Riktus are the most robust of the widespread Riktus family and this breastplate makes that very clear."};
