descriptions["11861"]={cn:"感受阿玛克纳的富饶吧。",en:"A powder as rich as Amakna."};
descriptions["11862"]={cn:"感受邦塔的苛刻吧。",en:"A powder as rigorous as Bonta."};
descriptions["11863"]={cn:"感受布拉克玛的愤怒。",en:"A powder as angry as Brakmar."};
descriptions["11864"]={cn:"感受萨弗基亚的速度。",en:"A powder as fast as Sufokia."};
descriptions["11865"]={cn:"小心使用。能轻易引起地震，赶走入侵者。",en:"Go careful when using this bow. It can cause earthquakes that shoot off the Richter."};
descriptions["11866"]={cn:"不服？来战。",en:"Let the standards of war be drawn!"};
descriptions["11867"]={cn:"奖励给最勇敢的土匪。",en:"This beautiful sword is awarded to the most courageous Riktus."};
descriptions["11868"]={cn:"挖的宝藏越多，你笑得越开心。",en:"Your smile grows wider with every piece of treasure you unearth!"};
descriptions["11869"]={cn:"保证你无法被忽视！",en:"This cloak makes sure you don\'t go unnoticed."};
descriptions["11870"]={cn:"盾牌上狰狞的笑脸很容易吸引敌人注意力。",en:"The daunting smile on this shield will conveniently distract your adversary."};
descriptions["11871"]={cn:"提供佩戴者坚韧之地。",en:"This ring grants its wearer great strength."};
descriptions["11872"]={cn:"提供佩戴者敏捷之风。",en:"This ring grants its wearer great agility."};
descriptions["11873"]={cn:"提供佩戴者智慧之火。",en:"This ring grants its wearer great intelligence."};
descriptions["11874"]={cn:"提供佩戴者幸运之水。",en:"This ring grants its wearer great chance."};
descriptions["11875"]={cn:"With a ring like this, your chances of ending up in a cage go down.",en:"With a ring like this, your chances of ending up in a cage go down."};
descriptions["11878"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["11880"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["11882"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["11886"]={cn:"这群海盗快把你逼疯了！",en:"All this chaos might send you loopy!"};
descriptions["11892"]={cn:"蓝色的口袋，轻如羽毛，紧贴你的腰带。",en:"A little blue pouch which is as light as a feather and will hook easily onto your belt."};
descriptions["11893"]={cn:"红色的口袋，轻如羽毛，紧贴你的腰带。",en:"A little red pouch which is as light as a feather and will hook easily onto your belt."};
descriptions["11894"]={cn:"绿色的口袋，轻如羽毛，紧贴你的腰带。",en:"A little green pouch which is as light as a feather and will hook easily onto your belt."};
descriptions["11895"]={cn:"紫色的口袋，轻如羽毛，紧贴你的腰带。",en:"A little purple pouch which is as light as a feather and will hook easily onto your belt."};
descriptions["11896"]={cn:"这是一个旧的包包。最好的办法是摆脱它，得到一个新的袋子！",en:"This bag is an old version. The best thing to do is to get rid of it and get a new bag!"};
descriptions["11897"]={cn:"这个袋子已经丑到扒手都没办法下手的地步了。",en:"This bag is so ugly that a pickpocket wouldn\'t go near it with a barge pole."};
descriptions["11898"]={cn:"对于容量而言这个袋子绝对是非常珍贵的，但是由于它易碎，因此请你小心保管。",en:"This bag is a real gem as far as capacity\'s concerned. But be careful with it, it\'ll break into pieces very easily."};
descriptions["11899"]={cn:"听起来像好吃的东西...其实只是个袋子。",en:"It sounds like some kind of delicious food... It\'s just a bag."};
descriptions["11900"]={cn:"散发着一股死鱼的臭气。",en:"This little pouch smells of rotten Snappers."};
descriptions["11901"]={cn:"这个小袋子依然很温暖，所以当你在外感觉寒冷的时候可以使用它来暖手。",en:"This little pouch is still warm, so you can use it to warm your hands when it\'s cold outside."};
descriptions["11902"]={cn:"这个女式背包带着一股玫瑰的气味。别闻得太使劲，当心被玫瑰味呛死。",en:"This girly little bag smells like roses, and will suffocate anyone who breathes in its vapors too deeply."};
descriptions["11903"]={cn:"你可以往口袋里塞菌菇，如果不喜欢菌菇也可以塞点别的什么。",en:"You can fill this sack with truffles, or with something else if you don\'t like truffles."};
descriptions["11904"]={cn:"不要对它有所顾忌，它不是真的骨骼所制，只是看起来可怕而已！",en:"Let\'s make no bones about it; it\'s not a real skull. That would just be horrible!"};
descriptions["11905"]={cn:"它的尺寸刚好够装下毛巾，防晒霜以及最近一期的绵球月刊。",en:"Just the right size for a towel, some sunblock and the latest issue of Gobbowl Monthly."};
descriptions["11906"]={cn:"完全由树叶制成。当心不要让它被风吹走了！",en:"This little pouch is made entirely of leaves. Careful it doesn\'t fly away!"};
descriptions["11907"]={cn:"你总是捡到小饰品以及吃了一半的巧克力。好吧，现在你有地方可以放了！",en:"You know how you\'re always stumbling upon little trinkets and half-eaten chocolate bars? Well now you have somewhere to put them!"};
descriptions["11908"]={cn:"这是一个旧的包包。最好的办法是摆脱它，得到一个新的袋子！",en:"This bag is an old version. The best thing to do is to get rid of it and get a new bag!"};
descriptions["11909"]={cn:"虽然看起来外表柔弱，但是这个袋子绝对是个坚韧难以被撕裂的好东西。",en:"Despite its delicate appearance, this bag is very hardy and difficult to rip."};
descriptions["11915"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["11918"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["11919"]={cn:"怎能不心动！",en:"Any excuse for Hazelnutella!"};
descriptions["11920"]={cn:"四月来临的时候，人们喜欢尝尝可口的绵球包。",en:"People eat these tasty Gobballs during the month of Aperirel."};
descriptions["11924"]={cn:"鹅肝只在重要场合才摆上餐桌。但是如果你想炫耀自己的身份，那么顿顿吃也可以。",en:"Normally Foie Gras is only eaten on special occasions, but if you want your friends to think you\'re a real aristocrat, why not serve it up for every meal?"};
descriptions["11925"]={cn:"在炎热的夏天里，让你头脑清醒。",en:"Cwab Pâté is a nice little dish to cool you down on those hot, sunny days."};
descriptions["11926"]={cn:"做这道菜只需要在油锅里把几块肉炸熟就好了。",en:"All there is to this dish is frying big lumps of fat in a well-oiled pan."};
descriptions["11927"]={cn:"放了很多糖、辣椒，以及一大堆好吃的东西，味道不错。",en:"Juicy Stew is a tasty dish full of sugar, spice and all things nice."};
descriptions["11928"]={cn:"看起来很可怕，所以闭上眼睛吃就是了。",en:"They look creepy, so just close your eyes and enjoy!"};
descriptions["11929"]={cn:"有一股淡淡的酸味，可以填饱肚子，让你有力气可以把世界背在身上，继续前进！",en:"This dish has a slightly sour taste, but it\'s incredibly filling and makes you feel strong enough to take on the World!"};
descriptions["11930"]={cn:"椰奶口感鲜美，饮用方便...但是无法提供每日所需的钙质。",en:"Kokomilk tastes delicious and can be easily slurped up with a straw... but it won\'t give you your daily portion of calcium."};
descriptions["11931"]={cn:"你从来没尝过泡泡奶？！现在就给你这个机会！",en:"What do you mean you\'ve never tried fizzy milk?! Now\'s your chance!"};
descriptions["11932"]={cn:"吃的时候加点盐...",en:"Take this Crab Pie with a pinch of salt..."};
descriptions["11934"]={cn:"有一种独特的鱼香味，让你沉醉在过往的美好回忆里。",en:"This cheese has a strange, fishy taste, but there\'s something about it that reminds you of the good old days, so you help yourself anyway."};
descriptions["11935"]={cn:"你喜欢满满的一盘鹌鹑配着酱汁吗？看它们在水池里幸福地泡着澡。",en:"If you like poultry and sauce then this dish will be like bathing in a pool of happiness."};
descriptions["11936"]={cn:"哪怕是个平民，也可以享受的美味。",en:"You don\'t have to be a nobleman to spread a bit of this exquisite pâté on a cracker and enjoy it with a glass of ice tea."};
descriptions["11939"]={cn:"承认吧，你只是因为免费玩具才喜欢这些的...",en:"Come on, you know you only like these because of the free toy..."};
descriptions["11940"]={cn:"支架是物品制作中的理想原料。通过0级工匠制作，可用于0-20级装备等用品制作。",en:"This bracket will help all your furniture hold on tight."};
descriptions["11945"]={cn:"这张门票允许你进入宝箱房间！很遗憾，你将无法和大怪物交手了。",en:"This ticket grants you access to the treasure room! Unfortunately, you won\'t be able to fight the dungeon Archmonster."};
descriptions["11946"]={cn:"这张门票允许你进入大怪物房间！很遗憾，你不得不放弃财宝了。",en:"This ticket grants you access to the Archmonster room! Unfortunately, you\'ll have to leave the dungeon\'s treasure behind."};
descriptions["11947"]={cn:"失去的才是最好的。",en:"Stolen Epaulettes are the sweetest."};
descriptions["11955"]={cn:"记住，咕咕要抓在手上才有价值。",en:"Remember, a Piwi in the hand is worth two in the bush."};
descriptions["12004"]={cn:"经过专业人士之手，湿木头马上显得亮丽光鲜。",en:"This damp wood can be really magnificent when it\'s carved by an expert."};
descriptions["12005"]={cn:"不能私自随意穿戴的头巾。很明显和土匪的一种重要仪式有关。",en:"You\'re not allowed to try this hood on yourself, but apparently it\'s used in a very important Riktus ritual."};
descriptions["12006"]={cn:"不能私自随意穿戴的头巾。很明显和土匪的一种重要仪式有关。",en:"You\'re not allowed to try this hood on yourself, but apparently it\'s used in a very important Riktus ritual."};
descriptions["12007"]={cn:"不能私自随意穿戴的头巾。很明显和土匪的一种重要仪式有关。",en:"You\'re not allowed to try this hood on yourself, but apparently it\'s used in a very important Riktus ritual."};
descriptions["12008"]={cn:"不能私自随意穿戴的头巾。很明显和土匪的一种重要仪式有关。",en:"You\'re not allowed to try this hood on yourself, but apparently it\'s used in a very important Riktus ritual."};
descriptions["12011"]={cn:"请置于喵喵以及骑士不可触及之处，当然也包括其他一切忍不住想玩帽子上的铃铛的人。",en:"Keep this hat as far away as possible from Bow Meows, Iops and all other beings that won\'t be able to resist the temptation to play with the bells."};
descriptions["12012"]={cn:"有趣的是这个领子只会让你显得更蠢。",en:"The funny thing is that this ruffle collar just makes you look stupid."};
descriptions["12013"]={cn:"没什么好笑的！滑稽可笑的外表让你自己成为笑料。",en:"This cloak is no laughing matter! The jolly, playful pattern makes sure that the joke is always on you."};
descriptions["12014"]={cn:"造型滑稽的鞋子，吓得你的敌人四处奔逃...鞋子上的铃铛能随时告诉敌人你要来讲要命的冷笑话了。",en:"These funny shoes will have your enemies running for cover - the bells will warn them that you\'re coming to tell them one of your jokes."};
descriptions["12015"]={cn:"不要被披风的外表欺骗了：一面由高质量100%纯绵球熟皮制成，另一面则是用生牛皮随便拼凑的。",en:"This cloak screams deception: one side is made of high-quality, 100% pure Gobball leather, the other of pieces of Moogrr skin thrown together any old how."};
descriptions["12016"]={cn:"天方夜谭头巾会让你头大！这尺寸足以塞40只喵喵进去！",en:"The Ally Baba Turban will topple you over! It\'s so large that you can fit 40 Bow Meows underneath!"};
descriptions["12017"]={cn:"这件短衣可以用来交换一盏从洞穴里发现的毫无用处的油灯，好主意哦！",en:"This tunic was exchanged for a useless, dusty oil lamp found in a cavern. Definitely a good deal, champ!"};
descriptions["12018"]={cn:"某个冒险者使劲摩擦肩甲，期望能冒出一个妖怪来。想吧，接着想。",en:"Certain adventurers will rub these epaulettes with the hope that a genie will appear. Keep on dreaming of genie and it might just happen."};
descriptions["12019"]={cn:"露出两只喵耳的可爱小帽！喵耳什么的真是太棒啦！",en:"Ths hat is so cute with its little Bow Meow ears! Some would give their head to have such a hat."};
descriptions["12020"]={cn:"好迷你，好可爱！真心受不了！",en:"A little top almost too cute to put on! Awww!"};
descriptions["12021"]={cn:"草莓味，嘎嘣脆！",en:"This little cloak is really cute and smells of yummy-scrummy strawberries!"};
descriptions["12022"]={cn:"无论面对什么样的挑战，这双靴子确保你造型完美...哪怕你只是在播种或者猎杀咕哩！",en:"These cute boots will give you a certain style and class whatever the task in hand - even if you\'re just sowing seeds or hunting Bliblis!"};
descriptions["12027"]={cn:"厚厚的一大本，记载着阿玛克纳的一切。",en:"A hefty volume containing all you need to know about Amakna."};
descriptions["12028"]={cn:"厚厚的一大本，记载着邦塔的一切。",en:"A hefty volume containing all you need to know about Bonta."};
descriptions["12029"]={cn:"厚厚的一大本，记载着布拉克玛的一切。",en:"A hefty volume containing all you need to know about Brakmar."};
descriptions["12030"]={cn:"厚厚的一大本，记载着萨弗基亚的一切。",en:"A hefty volume containing all you need to know about Sufokia."};
descriptions["12031"]={cn:"对骑士来说一无用处，不过对幸运猫而言，真是用来磨爪子的好家具！",en:"Completely useless for a Iop, but very practical for Ecaflips who want to buff down their nails!"};
descriptions["12032"]={cn:"由绵球下腹部的软毛做内衬。穿起来就像在云中漫步一样柔软舒适。",en:"These scrap iron boots have been generously stuffed with hairs from a Gobball\'s underbelly. As you can imagine, walking in them is as soft and fluffy as dancing on a cloud."};
descriptions["12033"]={cn:"天然、自由...！但是有少许虫蛀。",en:"So fresh, so free, so natural...! But kind of moth-eaten too."};
descriptions["12034"]={cn:"如果身处布拉克玛，那要当心了...它一点就着！你必须做好随时放出水系法术的准备。什么，不会水系法术？",en:"Take care if wearing this cape in Brakmar - it\'s highly flammable! Make sure you always have a Water spell handy, just in case."};
descriptions["12035"]={cn:"感觉像中了100万！",en:"It\'s in this amulet\'s nature to make its wearer feel like a million dollars!"};
descriptions["12036"]={cn:"戴起来舒适极了，完全不想取下。就算有木刺也不扎手！",en:"This ring feels so natural on that you\'ll never want to take it off. Even the splinters will start to feel like they\'re part of you!"};
descriptions["12037"]={cn:"百分百纯天然。保护皮肤中的益生菌，维持菌群平衡。当然，对于丑陋外貌并无改善作用。",en:"This wooden headband is 100% natural. It\'ll respect your skin\'s built-in bacteria and maintain its natural balance. In short, it\'ll do nothing for your monstrous appearance."};
descriptions["12038"]={cn:"产自邦塔的崭新护肩，让你双肩挺立。",en:"Freshly made in Bonta to perk up your shoulders."};
descriptions["12039"]={cn:"带静电的肩甲，所以你要在你做完头发之后再戴上他们。",en:"These epaulettes tend to create static electricity, so make sure you do your hair AFTER you\'ve put them on."};
descriptions["12040"]={cn:"充满了各种益生菌，增强你的抵抗力！",en:"This armor is full of bad bacteria, which will reinforce your natural defenses!"};
descriptions["12041"]={cn:"任何一个宝藏猎人都会告诉你他们再也不会制造这么划算的胸甲了！因为结实耐用又有型，它深受贫穷的冒险者喜爱。",en:"Any Enutrof will be quick to point out that they don\'t make trusty breastplates like this any more! Favored by adventurers who are short of cash, it\'s resistant and never goes out of style."};
descriptions["12042"]={cn:"提供的防御少得可怜。穿了跟没穿一样。",en:"This belt offers so little protection that you\'ll feel as naked with it on as you do with it off."};
descriptions["12043"]={cn:"从审美角度来讲，这条腰带一点也不漂亮。但是坚硬的锻钢会让敌人知道你的厉害。",en:"Aesthetically speaking, this belt isn\'t anything special, but the tempered iron it\'s made of will show your enemies that you\'re not to be messed with."};
descriptions["12044"]={cn:"其实和你手下穿的外套没多少差别，裁剪好一点吧，还有就是差不多贵一倍。穿上它你就不像是个新来的了，对吧？",en:"It\'s more or less the same as the jacket your disciples wear, but much better cut and at least twice as expensive. Don\'t want people thinking you\'re new around here, do ya?"};
descriptions["12045"]={cn:"这件披风太显眼，很远之外就能看到。如果你想收个学徒，那你得小心了，你没办法甩掉他。",en:"If you are planning on taking a disciple, choose carefully. You can be seen from afar in this cloak, so there\'ll be no getting away from him!"};
descriptions["12046"]={cn:"记住，越大的靴子意味着更重的责任：当心神出鬼没的狗仔队，一不小心就能让你名声扫地。",en:"Don\'t forget that big boots mean big responsibilities: watch out for the Bow Wow doo-doos or you will lose all credibility."};
descriptions["12051"]={cn:"带来好运的项链。",en:"Handmade by Sufokian stallion, Il Musselini, this necklace is said to bring luck in the local mafia\'s white-knuckled card tournaments. That could just be because of its distracting stench, though."};
descriptions["12052"]={cn:"空酒瓶会在战斗中骤然释放它的能量。",en:"This bottle is full of Frankfart\'s finest fizzy pop, and will release its energy in an explosive manner when you\'re in a bit of a hairy combat. Just be careful you don\'t end up doing the same...!"};
descriptions["12053"]={cn:"头上顶着一杯啤酒，每一天都是圣伯特里克节！",en:"With this mug of ginger ale balanced on your head at a jaunty angle, every day will feel like Saint Potrick\'s Day!"};
descriptions["12054"]={cn:"来点番茄酱和蒜末，味道更佳。哦啦啦！",en:"This cloak is just chipper with ketchup and garlic mayonnaise! Ooh la la!"};
descriptions["12055"]={cn:"来呀来呀，来咬我呀！等等，那真的是牛头人！它奔过来了！快逃！",en:"Andalay andalay! Areeba! Andalay! Wait... wait, is that a real Taur? It\'s coming towards you! Run! Run!"};
descriptions["12056"]={cn:"三色的腰带，质地牢固，把你和你的同伴牢牢捆在一起。",en:"This multi-functional belt helps hold you and all of your friends together in a cozy little group, and also prevents incontinence. Just make sure you don\'t slip out of the loop or you might find yourself all on your own in a puddle."};
descriptions["12057"]={cn:"为主人带来好运。",en:"In betwixt his afternoon teas, croquet and general larking about, local funnyman Mussel Grand had ample time to create yon shield. Say what you please about it, twill bounce right off."};
