descriptions["12098"]={cn:"起码这玩具不会像真的兔兔那样疯狂繁殖。",en:"At least this toy won\'t breed like real Wodents."};
descriptions["12100"]={cn:"宠物装备可以于宠物设定介面中更改。此物品已无用处，可以将其分解掉。",en:"Pet equipment can be changed in the pet settings interface. This item is obsolete; you can recycle it."};
descriptions["12101"]={cn:"巧克力做的剑，不能穿透敌人的护甲，却能融化敌人的心（啊呜呜）。",en:"This tough, chocolatey sword isn\'t much good at breaking through armor, but it might just melt your enemy\'s heart (aww)."};
descriptions["12102"]={cn:"想知道里面究竟藏了些什么？不告诉你...",en:"Wondering what\'s hidden underneath this helmet? Not telling... Surprise!"};
descriptions["12103"]={cn:"无比脆弱，大风天、晴天、雨天或者其他任何天气都不推荐使用。哪个蠢货想出来用巧克力做披风的？",en:"This cloak is incredibly fragile and not recommended for windy days, sunny days, rainy days, or any other day for that matter. Which smart Alec thought of making a chocolate cloak anyway?"};
descriptions["12104"]={cn:"没有什么比一块巧克力盾更能抵挡饿狼了。\n注意：切勿放置于阳光中暴晒。",en:"There\'s nothing better than a Chocolate Shield to defend from those ravenous attacks.\nNote: do not leave out in the sun."};
descriptions["12105"]={cn:"在上面蹲一会儿，能孵化出一只巧克力豆芙来。",en:"Apparently if you sit on the egg from this necklace, a chocolate Tofu will be born."};
descriptions["12106"]={cn:"你的双脚会慢慢融化在丝滑的巧克力里。嗯嗯，好味道！",en:"Your feet will melt deliciously into these silky boots. Mmmm, que bueno!"};
