descriptions["12126"]={cn:"和土耳其拖鞋高度相似。周围至少有四十个当地的毛贼盯着这双靴子。小心背后，否则你的下场会和火鸡节的火鸡一样。",en:"Closely resembling Turkish slippers, these boots are highly desired by at least forty of the local thieves in the neighborhood. Just watch your back or you might end up looking like a turkey."};
descriptions["12127"]={cn:"什么喵？",en:"How now Bow Meow?"};
descriptions["12128"]={cn:"趋于完美的喵宠物！他只比大多数喵喵暴躁、自私、懒惰一点点。知足吧，幸运儿！",en:"This Bow Meow is on the verge of perfection! He\'s very slightly less grumpy, selfish and lazy than most Bow Meows. Count yourself lucky!"};
descriptions["12129"]={cn:"好萌的小豆芙，好好吃的样子哦。",en:"A cuddly little Tofu that\'s so cute you could eat it!"};
descriptions["12130"]={cn:"这种豆芙有着三寸不烂之舌，可以用来教导骑士们怎么演讲。",en:"This tongue-twisting Tofu has served useful for many an elocution lesson for the Iops of this World."};
descriptions["12131"]={cn:"条纹喵是不同品种喵喵的混血后裔。喵专家们相信条纹喵比其他喵种更加聪明。",en:"Striped Bow Meows are all crossbreeds of several species of Bow Meow. Bow Meow specialists believe this species are a lot more intelligent and daring than the others."};
descriptions["12132"]={cn:"完美的花冠，让你看起来漂亮得像个公主。注意：请定期浇水以保证新鲜。",en:"The perfect tiara to make you feel like a princess. Note: water regularly to ensure optimum freshness."};
descriptions["12133"]={cn:"松紧度恰到好处！用于挑逗你的未来丈夫以及英俊的冒险者！",en:"It holds you in just where you need it! Perfect for titillating your future hubby, and all those other hunky adventurers too, of course!"};
descriptions["12134"]={cn:"如和风般轻盈，如细雨般柔软，自从穿上的那一天起就再也不想脱下。",en:"As light as the breeze and as soft as an Incarnam cloud, you wish you could wear this veil forever!"};
descriptions["12135"]={cn:"人们为这些易碎的、华丽的高跟拖鞋抢破头。自信点，你看起来漂亮极了。只是要当心别摔跤，别崴脚，然后真的摔破头！",en:"These high-heeled, extremely fragile, ornate slippers are to die for. Strut your stuff in confidence, knowing that you look the bomb. Just be careful you don\'t fall over, break your ankles and actually die in them!"};
descriptions["12136"]={cn:"始终保持简约精致，优雅时尚。许下你一声的承诺吧。",en:"Simple, refined, delicate and stylish all at the same time. You will want to commit yourself to it for life."};
descriptions["12137"]={cn:"除了金闪闪的纽扣之外，其实是很普通的一件衬衣。但是宝藏猎人可不会这么想！",en:"This shirt doesn\'t really have anything special about it other than its small golden buttons, but the Enutrofs can\'t get enough of it!"};
descriptions["12138"]={cn:"光鲜的燕尾服，人模企鹅样。",en:"A splendid tailcoat, so you can look handsome for your Pink Piwi and not too much like a Pingwin."};
descriptions["12139"]={cn:"婚姻如买鞋，没有的人拼命想买，拥有的人却想退货...实在太闷了。",en:"Persuading you to buy these shoes was easy - after all, they seemed so great in the shop! But now you\'ve got them on, they\'re so tight that you can\'t wait to get rid of them."};
descriptions["12140"]={cn:"尖头软鞋，将你的敌人送上不归路。",en:"Aggressive boots that will blast your enemies to the point of no return."};
descriptions["12141"]={cn:"用来插筷子的理想容器。作为帽子却没什么用。",en:"Ideal for holding your chopsticks. Useless as a hat."};
descriptions["12142"]={cn:"把你的一箩筐坏主意都藏里边吧。",en:"This turban is ideal for hiding the real you and your wicked ideas beneath."};
descriptions["12143"]={cn:"我们都有些不可告人的事，无论是糟糕的发型还是失败的晒伤妆。",en:"Cos we all have something to hide, from terrible haircuts to failed self-tanning sessions."};
descriptions["12144"]={cn:"十分显眼的头盔。战斗中，可以一眼就从军队里认出你。但是小心了：显眼可不是什么好事...",en:"This helmet is anything but inconspicuous. It will allow you to stand out from the crowd during battle. But watch out: nobody said that was a good thing..."};
descriptions["12145"]={cn:"幸运猫最喜欢这个头盔。事实上，喵喵们一点也不在乎。",en:"This fine model is particularly appreciated by the Ecaflips of the World but to be honest, the Bow Meows couldn\'t care less."};
descriptions["12146"]={cn:"和服！外国来的和服！哦哦哦哦哦！",en:"A kimono! From abroad! Ooooooooooooh!"};
descriptions["12147"]={cn:"看起来好像邪恶版本的阿里巴巴！",en:"Look like Baba\'s ally in this devious tunic!"};
descriptions["12148"]={cn:"很贵，而且不实用。",en:"This blazer is basically a white elephant - it has no real purpose and costs lots of money."};
descriptions["12149"]={cn:"保护你免受危险的海底生物侵扰，比如那些你经常听到的嗜血的、方头方脑的者喱。",en:"This armor protects you from dangerous sea creatures. Like those bloodthirsty, square, gelatinous monsters that you\'ve heard so much about."};
descriptions["12150"]={cn:"擦拭盔甲的时候，你会听到呜呜的喵叫。",en:"If you polish this armor you might just hear it purr."};
descriptions["12151"]={cn:"看起来像樱桃树的披风，据说可以让拥有者活得快乐长寿。",en:"This cherry-tree design cloak is supposed to bestow a long and happy life on whoever wears it."};
descriptions["12152"]={cn:"让人恶心的披风。它会不留情面地坑害你。小心了！",en:"An evil cloak that out-nasties even you. It will try relentlessly to do you wrong whenever it can. Watch your back!"};
descriptions["12153"]={cn:"你看起来有点傻，并且耳朵大得快让你飞上天了。",en:"Now just hold a magic feather in your nose and you\'ll be able to fly!"};
descriptions["12154"]={cn:"属于“真正”的冒险者！打一声响指它就能变成旗帜，吸引敌人来攻击你！",en:"A cloak of authentic adventurer! It changes into a flag at the snap of a castanet in order to attract more attention when on enemy soil."};
descriptions["12155"]={cn:"“血溅黑夜，红日初升”...曾经穿过这双靴子的弓手总喜欢向大家诉说靴子为什么这么红。",en:"\"The red sun rose... Blood had been spilled that night.\" - The Cra who used to wear these legwarmers loved telling everyone how they came to be red."};
descriptions["12156"]={cn:"你可以在其他人面前高昂着头颅，但是最终，你依然是个恶棍。",en:"You can try as you might to stand head over shoulders above the others but at the end of the day these are Dirty Scoundrel Epaulettes."};
descriptions["12157"]={cn:"让你每一步都倍感沉重。",en:"These shoes might make you a little heavy-footed."};
descriptions["12159"]={cn:"带有细小的倒刺，只要你想，就可以轻易刺伤你的敌人。",en:"These delicate boots are equipped with small claws that can scratch up your enemies just beautifully if you so choose."};
descriptions["12176"]={cn:"不要拒绝，否则...",en:"This costume makes you an offer you can\'t refuse."};
descriptions["12177"]={cn:"像俗话说得一样：现在你只是个学生，但是总有一天，你将变成老师。现在的老师一点也不在乎你有没有利用好你的时间。",en:"As the old saying goes, \"Now, you are but the learner. One day, you shall be the master.\" Your current master probably doesn\'t mind if you take your time."};
descriptions["12178"]={cn:"古老、被诅咒的戒指，自从前主人阵亡之后一直是无主之物。你能解开被封印其中的力量吗...？",en:"This old, cursed ring has broken free from the soul of its ex-master, who was killed in combat. Have you got what it takes to free the power held within...?"};
descriptions["12179"]={cn:"变成木乃伊吧！",en:"Enjoy yourself with Mummy! Mummy, Mummy Nova!"};
descriptions["12180"]={cn:"加入女武神行列吧！很威猛的！",en:"Join the Valkyrie army! You\'ve got the look!"};
descriptions["12181"]={cn:"根据阿玛克纳考古学家最新研究，这件披风也许属于某个秘密结社。",en:"It has been suggested that this cape, which was recently unveiled by Amaknian Arkaeologists, might be a sign of affiliation to a slightly secret society."};
descriptions["12182"]={cn:"好华丽的手绘装饰！骑士们是这么说的，你信吗？",en:"A magnificent, hand-painted, and very fragile ornament. Whatever you do, don\'t trust any Iops with it!"};
descriptions["12183"]={cn:"古老、被诅咒的武器，自从前主人阵亡之后一直是无主之物。你能解开被封印其中的力量吗...？",en:"This old, cursed weapon has broken free from the soul of its ex-master, who was killed in combat. Have you got what it takes to free the power held within...?"};
