descriptions["12202"]={cn:"残影犹在，身形已无。",en:"The art of being there without being there!"};
descriptions["12203"]={cn:"宠物装备可以于宠物设定介面中更改。此物品已无用处，可以将其分解掉。",en:"Pet equipment can be changed in the pet settings interface. This item is obsolete; you can recycle it."};
