descriptions["12207"]={cn:"做害羞状在生活中很有用，学着点！",en:"Acting shy can also have a diplomatic advantage in life - use it liberally!"};
descriptions["12208"]={cn:"为动不动就害羞并且容易受惊吓的人专门准备！",en:"For anyone who blushes easily and loves to let everyone know when they feel intimidated!"};
descriptions["12209"]={cn:"教你应对各种看起来不自然的生理本能反应...无论是熟睡、挑选美味佳肴还是看见漂亮的萨迪达少女的时候！",en:"This scroll will help you deal with all those uncomfortable yet natural moments - deep sleep, delectifying dishes, or even observing well-dressed Sadidettes!"};
descriptions["12210"]={cn:"肚子一饿就要发脾气？来叔叔下碗面给你吃。",en:"Get grumpy or aggressive when you\'re hungry? This scroll will allow you to hunger for something else."};
descriptions["12211"]={cn:"时髦的姿势，新人必学。还有什么能表现出你漠不关心的样子呢？",en:"Your most important scroll to date. What else could express your ultimate, all-encompassing apathy?"};
descriptions["12212"]={cn:"老师我会，老师看这里！",en:"Learn to say YES to life!"};
descriptions["12213"]={cn:"临时烧香，求神拜佛。",en:"This useful scroll will get you out of a lot of sticky situations. Solemn prayers work on gods, guild mates, and maybe even that precious Gobball that\'s chewing up your new cloak."};
descriptions["12214"]={cn:"没事的...人非圣贤。",en:"It\'s okay... We all mess up sometimes!"};
descriptions["12215"]={cn:"嘻嘻，真开心！",en:"Tell the World when you\'re having a magic moment!"};
descriptions["12216"]={cn:"宠物染料可以于宠物设定介面中更改。此物品已无用处，可以将其分解掉。",en:"Pet colorings can be changed in the pet settings interface. This item is obsolete; you can recycle it."};
