descriptions["12228"]={cn:"多亏了这块糖果，你的宠物可以很长时间不进食了。\n（持续一周）",en:"Thanks to this candy, your pet can go without food for a bit longer.\n(Lasts one week)"};
descriptions["12230"]={cn:"拿两张骨牌相互剐蹭，发出的刺耳响声足以恶心死骸骨之王。",en:"Scraping these cards against one another creates a high, grinding sound, piercing enough to wake a Chafer."};
descriptions["12231"]={cn:"能兑换一个稀有珍贵的物品！去阿斯图布的地窖一探究竟吧！",en:"This Little Round Token will win you a rare and precious item! Get down to the inn in Astrub to find out more!"};
descriptions["12232"]={cn:"出自一位非常聪明的糖果师的配方，会将他本人的一部分知识传递给你。",en:"This candy was inspired by a very wise confectioner\'s recipe book and will transfer part of his knowledge to you."};
descriptions["12233"]={cn:"入口即化。口味丝滑纯正。",en:"This candy tastes as sweet as a snuggle. Embrace the taste."};
descriptions["12234"]={cn:"不仅强身健体，还能提高物质富裕度。",en:"This candy will not only improve your well-being, but also your material wealth."};
descriptions["12235"]={cn:"为你的冒险带来好运和成功。好运气总是垂青勇敢的人。前进吧。",en:"This candy will bring you chance and success in everything you decide to sink your teeth into. They don\'t say fortune favors the brave for nothing. Go get \'em."};
descriptions["12237"]={cn:"活泼爱闹的小家伙。贝老太上了年纪管不住它了。她把小果冻交给你，作为冒险旅途上的陪伴。",en:"This little Gemlin is full of life and very boisterous. Since Mammy Pal\'s not that young anymore, she gave it to you so that it could accompany you on your adventures."};
descriptions["12240"]={cn:"宠物染料可以于宠物设定介面中更改。此物品已无用处，可以将其分解掉。",en:"Pet colorings can be changed in the pet settings interface. This item is obsolete; you can recycle it."};
descriptions["12241"]={cn:"这对护肩中的一只让你昏昏欲睡。另一只让你整天精神奕奕，准备着参加祭典！",en:"One of these epaulettes makes you sleepy enough for a siesta. The other makes you wide awake and ready for fiesta!"};
descriptions["12242"]={cn:"对于烂番茄和烂菜皮并没有防御效果。",en:"Naturally, it offers no protection against laughing fits and rogue custard pies."};
descriptions["12243"]={cn:"屁股扭起来，脚步迈起来。苍茫的天涯是我的爱，绵绵的青山脚下花正开...",en:"Shake your butt, watch your step, shake your butt, show me what you\'re working with...!"};
descriptions["12245"]={cn:"不向任何人屈服，就算是你也不例外！",en:"This bow will bow to nobody - not even you!"};
descriptions["12246"]={cn:"很明显，属于某个阿玛克纳110救火队员。他们用尽全力才扑灭了由一个粗鲁混蛋故意纵火造成的火灾。上面仍然残留有明显的火灾的痕迹。",en:"Apparently, this staff belonged to one of the 110 Amaknian firefighters it took to put out the fire started deliberately by the reckless Red Wyrmling. There were definite signs of arson about."};
descriptions["12247"]={cn:"你值得拥有。",en:"Because you\'re worth... something. Maybe."};
descriptions["12256"]={cn:"滑稽可笑的锤子，被敌人看到了，他们会捧腹大笑。这样一来就为你赢得了攻其不备的机会。笑到最后的会是你。",en:"This Hammer is so ridiculous that your enemy will burst out laughing the minute he sets eyes on you. The time gained by this diversion should let you have the last laugh, though."};
descriptions["12257"]={cn:"任何一个名符其实的宝藏猎人都留着满脸的胡子，老克里·诺希夫也不例外。有一天他的妻子，诺希夫太太为他买了一把剃须刀，他觉得还是拿来当作武器比较好...",en:"Any Enutrof worthy of the name has a beard, and old Krys Nosheive was no exception. One day his wife, Mrs Nosheive, bought him a razor, and he decided he would rather use it as a weapon..."};
descriptions["12258"]={cn:"你大可以吹嘘说这把斧头可以裂天碎地。吹，接着吹。",en:"You can claim that this can slice the sky, but you\'ll just be blowing hot air."};
descriptions["12259"]={cn:"如果你对于腐尸的气味毫不在意，那么这根棍子肯定能满足你的各种变态需求。",en:"If you can get over the deathly stench, this club is sure to satisfy your more morbid urges."};
descriptions["12260"]={cn:"由伟大的卡尔·格劳乔制造，他是痞子联盟的守护者。他在他的墓碑上刻上了他的名言“经验使人上瘾”。",en:"This sword was made by the great Karl Groucho, defender of the Hoglians. He engraved his famous maxim in its side: \"XP is the opium of the people.\""};
descriptions["12261"]={cn:"发明这把武器的匠人收了不少徒弟。他经常会想不起来他要说些什么。看起来他并不是个好老师...",en:"The artisan who invented this wand had apprentices to train. Not the greatest teacher in the World, he often couldn\'t keep his mind on what he was saying long enough to finish the..."};
descriptions["12262"]={cn:"即便你浑身全是破布，这把铲子也能让你举止优雅。皇帝一向只穿新装！",en:"Even if you\'re dressed in rags, this shovel will make you seem elegant and refined. Whatever happened to calling a spade a spade?"};
descriptions["12277"]={cn:"趟过泥水沼泽，饱经风霜。它散发着一股发霉的烂泥气息，时不时地刺激你的鼻子。",en:"This costume seems to have weathered both winds and tides. It\'s also retained a subtle scent of must that shuffles its way into your nostrils on a regular basis."};
descriptions["12278"]={cn:"漂亮的假发，它原来的主人胃口极大。\n想有漂亮的卷发，请每天至少吃5个冒险者！",en:"This beautiful hair\'s original owner had a biiig appetite.\nFor curly hair, eat at least 5 adventurers a day!"};
descriptions["12279"]={cn:"是的，你看起来酷毙了...现在去打劫吧！",en:"Yes, you look cool - now go get some booty!"};
descriptions["12284"]={cn:"使你的宠物恢复1点生命。",en:"This powder will restore a pet\'s HP by 1."};
descriptions["12285"]={cn:"手工雕刻的龙龟蛋，水龙蛋的复制品。",en:"This hand-carved Turquoise Dofus is a perfect wooden replica of Aguabrial\'s Dofus."};
descriptions["12286"]={cn:"我会从过去的时间里讨回遗产！以杰克之名发誓！",en:"I\'ve got a relic from times gone by! Jack my swag!"};
descriptions["12287"]={cn:"你迫不及待地穿上先驱时装，事实上，它比你还急！",en:"As if you weren\'t eager enough to slip into your Pioneer clothes, this costume will help you do so even faster!"};
descriptions["12288"]={cn:"宠物染料可以于宠物设定介面中更改。此物品已无用处，可以将其分解掉。",en:"Pet colorings can be changed in the pet settings interface. This item is obsolete; you can recycle it."};
descriptions["12324"]={cn:"金黄松脆的饼乾...令人馋涎欲滴！能喂给某些地下城里的宝箱怪获得奖励，譬如说云朵羊毛！",en:"Krumbly kibble to nibble is enough to make you dribble! Can be fed to Mimics in certain dungeons. Could be rewarding, like Cloudy Cotton!"};
descriptions["12325"]={cn:"天黑黑，下大雨。老头在吐口水！为你特意准备！",en:"It\'s raining, it\'s pouring, the old Mimik is slobbering. This solidified slobber can be used to stick items together to make tools."};
descriptions["12329"]={cn:"它杀了所有人，甚至是它的主人...让人想起那个只知道滥用管理员指令的家伙，他甚至都不知道那些指令是什么意思...",en:"Well yeah, it kills everything, even the person who uses it (badly)... A bit like the guy who pops out admin commands but doesn\'t know what they mean..."};
descriptions["12330"]={cn:"[ADMIN] 测试必杀指令。",en:"[ADMIN] A sword for testing KO stuff on carried characters."};
descriptions["12332"]={cn:"[ADMIN] 足足一百个格子，开心吧？！",en:"[ADMIN] \nA 100 slot bag. Splendid!"};
descriptions["12333"]={cn:"我想...你最好别把面具摘下来！",en:"You\'d be better just keeping this mask on, I think...!"};
descriptions["12334"]={cn:"如果你想不出什么好主意，你可以拿这对护肩往墙上扔，或者往敌人身上扔。",en:"If you are short of ideas, you could always use these epaulettes to smash up walls as well as your enemies."};
descriptions["12335"]={cn:"第一眼看上去好像轻如羽毛。实际上重得跟砖块一样。使劲！",en:"At first glance, this breastplate seems as light as a feather. In reality it\'s as heavy as a sack of bricks. Make sure you buff up before attempting to put it on!"};
descriptions["12336"]={cn:"十分朴素的靴子，晚上溜出去一点都不会引人注意。",en:"These boots are so discreet they\'ll allow you to step out at night without getting caught."};
descriptions["12337"]={cn:"刻有十二世界中罪大恶极之人的标记。",en:"This ring is stricken with the trademark of the dirtiest Bandits in the World of Twelve."};
descriptions["12338"]={cn:"如果你被冰山困住了，这件披风可以提供助你脱困的热气流。",en:"This cloak has thermal elements which will help you out if you ever get stuck on a glacier."};
descriptions["12339"]={cn:"一触碰到其他剑，就会发出令人毛骨悚然的刺耳笑声。",en:"As soon as this sword crosses with another it emits a piercing, metallic-sounding cackle."};
descriptions["12340"]={cn:"不服？来战。",en:"Hold this flagpole high with pride. Let the colours of the bandit elite shine on!"};
descriptions["12341"]={cn:"自动发射箭矢，根本不需要费一点力气。",en:"Don\'t lift a finger, the arrow will launch itself!"};
descriptions["12342"]={cn:"用来攻击比防御好多了。",en:"This shield is better at biffing and bashing than blocking."};
descriptions["12343"]={cn:"[ADMIN] 复活被击杀的角色。",en:"[ADMIN] Sword to revive a KO\'d character."};
descriptions["12346"]={cn:"献给创生之力的信徒。",en:"For those who believe in the power of Wakfu."};
descriptions["12347"]={cn:"阴险的利刃，时刻寻找着背后补刀的机会。",en:"These sneaky blades always find just the right moment to attack from behind."};
descriptions["12348"]={cn:"不要担心匕首从哪里飞来。它们实在是太滑了！",en:"Don\'t worry about where these daggers came from, or the fact that their handles seem to be a bit \"slippery\"!"};
descriptions["12349"]={cn:"这个匕首对于止疼有着惊人的效果，非常适合那些不想听到他们对手哭泣的人佩戴，那些觉得它很有趣的家伙们实在太坏了。",en:"This dagger has the specific property of preventing pain. Ideal for those who hate to hear their opponents cry. Too bad for those who find it amusing."};
descriptions["12350"]={cn:"由酒馆招牌制成的护盾，能保证你不头痛，大概是这样...恩，没错的。",en:"This shield, made from a tavern sign, will make sure you don\'t get any headaches, but that\'s about it."};
descriptions["12351"]={cn:"由酒馆招牌制成的护盾，能保证你不头痛，大概是这样...恩，没错的。",en:"This shield, made from a tavern sign, will make sure you don\'t get any headaches, but that\'s about it."};
descriptions["12352"]={cn:"由酒馆招牌制成的护盾，能保证你不头痛，大概是这样...恩，没错的。",en:"This shield, made from a tavern sign, will make sure you don\'t get any headaches, but that\'s about it."};
descriptions["12353"]={cn:"不放心自己辛辛苦苦挣来的卡玛的人有福了。有了此盾，他们大可安心。",en:"This is great for those who want to look after their hard-earned kamas. Finally, a shield made for the well-off!"};
descriptions["12354"]={cn:"不放心自己辛辛苦苦挣来的卡玛的人有福了。有了此盾，他们大可安心。",en:"This is great for those who want to look after their hard-earned kamas. Finally, a shield made for the well-off!"};
descriptions["12355"]={cn:"不放心自己辛辛苦苦挣来的卡玛的人有福了。有了此盾，他们大可安心。",en:"This is great for those who want to look after their hard-earned kamas. Finally, a shield made for the well-off!"};
descriptions["12356"]={cn:"你成就了奥古行者。恭喜！",en:"You have proved yourself as a true Ogrestinator. Congratulations!"};
descriptions["12357"]={cn:"当心半夜里被咬一口。",en:"Careful with this amulet. It might just bite you in the middle of the night."};
descriptions["12358"]={cn:"献给喜欢爽爽快快完成工作的人！",en:"For those that like to get a job done and dusted!"};
descriptions["12359"]={cn:"当你与狼共舞的时候，这双靴子可以让你轻松一点儿。",en:"These boots will make it that little bit easier to dance with Boowolves."};
descriptions["12360"]={cn:"听到有人喊“狼来了”，请逃命！",en:"The day someone cries Boowolf is the day you should run for your life!"};
descriptions["12361"]={cn:"由最柔软的狼毛制成。",en:"This belt is made from the softest Boowolf hairs around."};
descriptions["12362"]={cn:"把毛刮干净...每逢满月，肩膀上的狼毛又会长出来...比之前的毛长一倍！",en:"Shave away... Just remember that every full moon the hairs on these epaulettes will grow back... and twice as thick as before!"};
descriptions["12363"]={cn:"一个人走夜路时记得带着这枚护符。",en:"This lucky amulet will protect you from those uneasy midnight encounters."};
descriptions["12364"]={cn:"在森林里穿会显得很可怕，能展现你隐藏的狂野一面。",en:"This mask can be pretty terrifying\nif worn in the forestand will really bring out your wild side."};
descriptions["12365"]={cn:"穿上它，变身披着狼皮的羊。",en:"You\'ll be like a sheep in Boowolf\'s clothing with this cloak made from real Boowolf skin."};
descriptions["12366"]={cn:"你真走运！你的敌人气愤得咬牙切齿，还没开打你已经占据优势。",en:"You lucky dog! This club sets your adversaries\' teeth on edge and puts you in good stead for a beastly battle."};
descriptions["12367"]={cn:"看起来像是满月教徒的法杖。",en:"This weapon seems to be the staff of choice for the lunar ritual."};
descriptions["12368"]={cn:"独一无二的戒指，然而你并不是戴它的唯一人选。",en:"This ring is unique, but you\'re not the only one to wear it."};
descriptions["12369"]={cn:"这双靴子让你向后倒退的时候十分轻松...而且很有型！",en:"These boots make walking backwards that little bit easier... and so much more stylish!"};
descriptions["12370"]={cn:"孩子们都喜欢这双靴子...夜里迈出的每一步都散发出皎洁的月光。",en:"All the kids LOVE these boots - they\'re the kind that light up with every step you take. We know, we know, you used to have a pair..."};
descriptions["12371"]={cn:"带你飞向月球，才怪。",en:"Unfortunately it won\'t fly you to the moon, nor let you play among the stars."};
descriptions["12372"]={cn:"满月在手，世界我有。\n恩，虽然只有一点点。",en:"They say he\'s got the whole World in his hands, but it looks like you\'ve got the moon! \nWell, a bit of it, at least."};
descriptions["12373"]={cn:"在月光下熠熠发光。",en:"This breastplate glows in the moonlight."};
descriptions["12374"]={cn:"对于喜欢睡懒觉的人来说，这个护符晚上可以把你闪醒。",en:"This amulet is a surprisingly effective night-light for those times when you just can\'t get off."};
descriptions["12375"]={cn:"华丽地致命一击，让敌人永眠。",en:"Put your enemies to sleep with one fatal blow from this marvelous blade."};
descriptions["12376"]={cn:"这些小刀片只有在满月的时候才能杀杀狼，其他时候是完全绝对没有用的。",en:"These little blades only slice up Boowolves when there is a full moon. The rest of the time they\'re completely and utterly useless."};
descriptions["12377"]={cn:"畜生禁用。",en:"Not for brutes."};
descriptions["12378"]={cn:"点击两下来把整组古代资源转换成新的资源。古代资源需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["12379"]={cn:"据说每次有狼死去，月亮都会流下一滴眼泪...准备好纸巾。",en:"It is often said that the moon sheds a tear each time a Boowolf is killed... Have your tissues at the ready."};
descriptions["12381"]={cn:"只需一击就可以让巨魔昏迷不醒。问题是，你拿得起来吗？",en:"One blow of this club is enough to decapitate a Trool. The question is, are you strong enough to pick it up?"};
descriptions["12382"]={cn:"每走一小步，腰带上的小铃铛都会剧烈摇动，任何人都会察觉到你在偷偷接近。漂亮和惊喜二选一。",en:"The little bells that adorn this belt jingle so violently that they make it impossible to sneak up on anyone. Look, it was either style or surprise. You can\'t have both!"};
descriptions["12383"]={cn:"铃儿响叮当。",en:"Hell\'s bells, this amulet is gorgeous!"};
descriptions["12384"]={cn:"别戴得太紧！",en:"Don\'t tighten it too much, now!"};
descriptions["12385"]={cn:"虽然披着狼皮的你看起来像禽兽，不过真的很暖和！",en:"It\'ll keep you nice and warm, even if you do look quite beastly!"};
descriptions["12386"]={cn:"其他人看起来还以为一头幼狼啃掉了你的头，然后趴在你背后！",en:"This headgear will give onlookers the impression that a Milimoowolf ate you up and spat you straight back out again!"};
