descriptions["12407"]={cn:"重量和一头死去的哞哞差不多，能防水防狼。有时候，巨魔们甚至将它用作镜子。",en:"The Foolmoun weighs about as much as a dead Moogrr, but it\'s waterproof and resistant to Boowolf scratches. Sometimes, Trools even use it as a mirror."};
