descriptions["12422"]={cn:"会绕上你的脖子，让你难以喘息。是杀死仇敌的极佳武器。",en:"This wand can tighten itself round your neck to strangle you. A very notable way to kill those you have little respect for."};
descriptions["12424"]={cn:"最初用来在茂密丛林里砍树的双刃剑。有一天伐木工突然发现它是一把强有力的兵器。",en:"This double blade was originally used to cut down trees in dense forests. The lumberjacks soon realized that it could also be make a very powerful weapon."};
descriptions["12425"]={cn:"射月摘星如探囊取物。",en:"This bow is powerful enough to send an arrow to the moon."};
descriptions["12426"]={cn:"穿起来舒服极了，你挑不出任何毛病来。可是如果你打算把这双靴子拱手让给敌人，他们可不会知足。",en:"These shoes are so comfortable, you can\'t help but be satisfied with them. Your enemies might not be quite so content if you decide to give them the boot, though."};
descriptions["12427"]={cn:"无拘无束的披风，注定流浪一生。",en:"A free-thinking, radical cloak, destined for a bohemian lifestyle."};
descriptions["12428"]={cn:"和它的主人一样，这件披风经常被人轻视。它由绿色异种虫皮制成，质地粗糙。",en:"This cloak is, just like its owner, often underestimated. It is made from green larva skins, which gives even the nicest people a rough side."};
descriptions["12429"]={cn:"穿上披风，变身博学之士。",en:"Pop on this cloak and you\'ll feel like a right know-it-all."};
descriptions["12430"]={cn:"准备好成为火箭科学家吧。",en:"Just enough to make you a rocket scientist."};
descriptions["12431"]={cn:"疯兔并不仅仅是你想象中的温柔可爱的小动物。这些野蛮的动物会为了一杯胡萝卜汁，用它们的盾牌把胡萝卜压得粉碎。",en:"Wabbits aren\'t the sweet, cuddly little creatures you like to think they are. These barbaric animals will crush a Cawwot with their shield, just to make a glass of juice."};
descriptions["12432"]={cn:"鸵鸟袋？或者是关于鸵鸟的袋子？\n这是个好问题...",en:"Strich Bag? Or Bag of Strich?\nThat is the question..."};
descriptions["12433"]={cn:"尽管叫这名字，这把斧头根本不能用来砍树。如果你够强壮能拿得起它，就去找只兽人试试身手，包你满意。",en:"Despite its name, this axe is no good at chopping down trees. If you\'re strong enough to lift it, try it on a Bwork and you should get much more satisfying results."};
descriptions["12434"]={cn:"在碎石者身上自然生长。十分柔软，遇上险恶的天气或者倒霉的事故还能有效缓冲。",en:"This moss grows naturally on Cracklers. It is soft and ultra-absorbent in case of inclement weather or embarrassing accidents."};
descriptions["12435"]={cn:"碎石者喜欢将钻石像小石头一样丢来丢去玩。这足够让你发疯了！",en:"Cracklers tend to throw this highly sought-after diamond around as if it were a pebble. Just enough to make you snap!"};
descriptions["12436"]={cn:"看起来破破烂烂，但是能让你安然无恙。",en:"This helmet might look pretty beat-up but there\'s some life in it yet."};
descriptions["12437"]={cn:"来吧，穿着它踏碎地面！",en:"Go on, have a crack at walking in these!"};
descriptions["12438"]={cn:"亲爱的，它碎掉了。",en:"This ring is absolutely cracking, dahling."};
descriptions["12439"]={cn:"不要在肩甲的重压下崩溃。",en:"Make sure you don\'t crack under the strain of these epaulettes."};
descriptions["12440"]={cn:"由岩石制成的面具。好吧，你还指望些什么？",en:"This mask is made of stone. Well, what did you expect?"};
descriptions["12441"]={cn:"坚如磐石！",en:"This ring is solid... Solid as a... Oh."};
descriptions["12442"]={cn:"有点重，不便于随身携带。但是可以用来把人敲晕。",en:"They\'re not exactly light and they\'re kind of difficult to carry around, but these cards are still practical for knocking somebody senseless."};
descriptions["12443"]={cn:"别想过去！",en:"You shall not pass!"};
descriptions["12444"]={cn:"很重，但是你还是想戴着它！",en:"It\'s heavy but that\'s not going to stop you wearing it!"};
descriptions["12445"]={cn:"只要你能拿起来，就能狠狠打痛敌人。",en:"This hammer hits hard, if you can pick it up."};
descriptions["12446"]={cn:"如果你需要学习如何放慢你的脚步，这双鞋对你来说是在好不过的选择，它会让你的肌肉没有时间休息，不过如果我是你，我绝对不会试图穿着它游泳。",en:"Once you\'ve learned to stop dragging your feet, these clogs will build up your calf muscles in no time. If I were you, though, I wouldn\'t wear them swimming."};
descriptions["12447"]={cn:"好吧，你根本不用担心它会被吹走。但是万一它砸下来，你会被砸扁。",en:"Well, you don\'t have to worry about it blowing away in the wind, but if it falls over, you risk being crushed like a pancake."};
descriptions["12448"]={cn:"用于挖掘大石块，挖小碎石也很有效。",en:"Great for digging up large stones and little Crackrocks."};
descriptions["12450"]={cn:"能去除足部干燥的死皮。只要你喜欢，也可以在战斗中使用。",en:"This stone is great for removing dead, dry skin from the soles of your feet. You can even use it in battle, if you like!"};
descriptions["12451"]={cn:"别担心，还能穿很多年。",en:"Don\'t worry, it\'ll last for years yet."};
descriptions["12454"]={cn:"让羽毛飞一会儿！",en:"You\'ll be able to make the feathers fly with this ring!"};
descriptions["12455"]={cn:"由顶级乌鸦羽毛制成。",en:"Made with top-quality Crobak feathers."};
descriptions["12456"]={cn:"不...这并不意味着你是跆拳道高手...只是给你装装样子而已。",en:"No... This belt does NOT mean that you are a master in martial arts... it might make you feel like one, though!"};
descriptions["12457"]={cn:"乌鸦羽毛嵌在了戒指里，看起来漆黑一团。",en:"Crobak feathers have tainted this ring, hence its dark, dark color."};
descriptions["12458"]={cn:"长长的鸦羽，不断刺激你发笑。",en:"These epaulettes are so feathery they\'ll almost make you gaga!"};
descriptions["12459"]={cn:"木质的魔杖里藏着一根乌鸦羽毛。当地人盛传只要使用得当，你就能获得不屈的意志。",en:"Within this wooden wand is a beautiful Crobak feather. The locals say that, used correctly, it might just give you more quillpower and make you more determined."};
descriptions["12460"]={cn:"是的，帽子上确实有一只死乌鸦...不久之前的空难！",en:"Yes, that dead Crobak on this helmet is real... It was all the rage not so long ago!"};
descriptions["12461"]={cn:"好比带了一只鸟在脖子上。它可不会保护你。",en:"Wearing this amulet is a bit like having a great big bird around your neck, which is why it won\'t really protect you from baddies."};
descriptions["12462"]={cn:"所有迷信的敌人都会吓得发抖。",en:"This hand will make all your superstitious adversaries wince in fear."};
descriptions["12463"]={cn:"并不是最牢的袋子，但是内部空间很宽裕。",en:"This feathery bag isn\'t the most resistant but it\'s surprisingly spacious inside."};
descriptions["12464"]={cn:"乌鸦肉浸泡在融化的乳酪中。世上还有更美味的东西吗？",en:"Crobak meat smothered in melted cheese. Is there anything finer?"};
descriptions["12465"]={cn:"乌鸦领主经常叼着这块奶酪在他的树上休息。奶酪气味好闻极了，你满脑子都想着要吃掉它。",en:"Lord Crow is often perched in his tree holding this delicious cheese gently in his beak. It smells so good you can think of nothing else but eating it."};
descriptions["12466"]={cn:"锋利的匕首，背刺利器。",en:"This Crobak feather is pretty darn sharp and comes in handy for back-stabbing."};
descriptions["12467"]={cn:"我一直以为乌鸦是黑的，直到我膝盖中了一箭。",en:"This arc has a large range and launches as the crow flies."};
descriptions["12469"]={cn:"点击两下来把整组古代资源转换成新的资源。古代资源需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["12470"]={cn:"冒险者坚信，蓝星是由死去的星魔转世而成的。",en:"Adventurers believe this to be the reincarnation of a dead Gobgob."};
descriptions["12471"]={cn:"鞋面上布满了蓝色星星，带你进入梦想之地。",en:"You\'re sure to be happy with these boots. They\'re covered in blue stars and foot the bill perfectly for walking on air!"};
descriptions["12472"]={cn:"想摘星星的话，只要轻敲披风即可。呼吸之间，它已爬上高山。",en:"If you want to reach for the stars, just chuck on this cloak. It might even help you climb every mountain."};
descriptions["12473"]={cn:"仿佛置身于云朵之中...事实上...你置身于...星辰...",en:"It\'s like having your head in the clouds... except that... it\'s in the...  stars..."};
descriptions["12474"]={cn:"让你开怀大笑！",en:"This ring will make you twinkle with joy!"};
descriptions["12475"]={cn:"能找到这件胸甲你真走运！",en:"You can thank your lucky star you\'ve found this breastplate!"};
descriptions["12476"]={cn:"它总是唠唠叨叨、口若悬河，敌人几乎被烦死了。",en:"This axe has always got something to say, and your enemies are almost definitely going to end up with a headache."};
descriptions["12477"]={cn:"对于唤兽师来说十分好用的锤子。但是其他人就难说了。小心手指被咬断...",en:"Very useful for Osamodas, among others... Just watch your fingers."};
descriptions["12479"]={cn:"你将会是下一个幸运之星。",en:"A whack from this sword will hit your enemies like a bolt from the blue."};
descriptions["12480"]={cn:"据说这副眼镜能让你鸟瞰一切。但愿这只鸟不是近视眼！",en:"They say that this monocle allows you to see everything with a bird\'s-eye view. Here\'s hoping the bird in question wasn\'t short-sighted!"};
descriptions["12481"]={cn:"让敌人眼冒星星。",en:"Use this shield to defend yourself and you\'ll leave your adversaries seeing stars!"};
descriptions["12482"]={cn:"天堂之门为你打开。",en:"Hitch your Dragoturkey to a star and open every door of opportunity with this key."};
descriptions["12483"]={cn:"保证让你浑身柔软！",en:"The Black Crow\'s Feather will make sure you always have a bit of fluff!"};
descriptions["12484"]={cn:"成为黑暗的主人，为自己的力量颤抖吧！",en:"Become the master of darkness and fear your own strength!"};
descriptions["12486"]={cn:"这双拖鞋舒适极了...现在你知道卡波克总是宅在他自己店里的原因了！",en:"These slippers are super-duper snuggly... Now you know why Kabrok is always doing the shuffle in his shop!"};
descriptions["12487"]={cn:"你可以学史努福戴上铃铛，但是这并不意味着你会找到一屋子的卡玛...",en:"You might be wearing bells like a Snoofle, but that doesn\'t mean the kamas are going to start rolling in..."};
descriptions["12488"]={cn:"不要忘了放松一点头盔带...否则脱下来的时候就难了！",en:"Don\'t forget to unfasten the leather straps that hold this helmet to your head.... It might be a bit difficult to take off otherwise!"};
descriptions["12489"]={cn:"只有世界上最强的勇士才能染指的宝剑，以宝石镶嵌，闪烁着神秘的光辉。",en:"A beautifully-decorated black sword that only the hardest of the World\'s warriors can control."};
descriptions["12491"]={cn:"漂亮的白色名牌包。有 30 格空间。",en:"A beautiful, white, name-brand bag with 30 spaces."};
descriptions["12492"]={cn:"漂亮的红色名牌包。有 20 格空间。",en:"A beautiful, red, name-brand bag with 20 spaces."};
descriptions["12493"]={cn:"漂亮的黑色名牌包。\n还有其它款式可供选择。",en:"A beautiful, black, name-brand bag with 10 spaces."};
descriptions["12505"]={cn:"使用滚烫的咖啡制成，给敌人好好来一下，让他不会轻易忘记它。",en:"Made from boiling cwoffee, a good hit from this blade, and your enemies won\'t easily forget it."};
descriptions["12509"]={cn:"是什么样的设计让它将花开的瞬间定格住，使得它有如此魅力，你无法阻止我们前进的道路！",en:"What makes it so captivating is the ingenious method devised to stop the flower wilting. Technology never ceases to amaze!"};
descriptions["12511"]={cn:"主要用来防晒。现在这些哞哞再也不可能变得黑白相间，白里透红了！",en:"A perfect hat to protect against sunburn. There\'s no chance these Moogrrs will be black and white and red all over now!"};
descriptions["12512"]={cn:"如果你想乱花钱，那么这是你应该买的。它能让你成为万人景仰之人！",en:"If you\'re looking for something to blow your money on, this is an absolute must-have. It\'ll make you the toast of the taverns!"};
descriptions["12513"]={cn:"使劲嚼...嚼个几十年...\n提高伐木技能。",en:"Chew it... For ages...\nImproves lumberjack skills."};
descriptions["12514"]={cn:"能凸显你美妙曲线的肩垫，让你美丽一百分！",en:"Garments that accentuate your curves and make you look just spectacular."};
descriptions["12515"]={cn:"粘有大量臭气熏天的哞哞荷尔蒙，能让哞群整天不安分。",en:"These epaulettes have been sprayed with horrendous stinking Moogrr pheromones and will therefore keep Moogrrs on heat at bay."};
descriptions["12516"]={cn:"刚开始有一点痛，但是如果能撑住，你会发现它们漂亮极了！",en:"You might find that these epaulettes press a little on your shoulders but if you can stand the pain you\'ll soon feel the supremacy!"};
descriptions["12517"]={cn:"但愿你牙齿足够强健。\n提高采矿技能。",en:"I hope you\'ve got strong jaws.\nImproves miner skills."};
descriptions["12518"]={cn:"养成健壮的骨骼。\n提高种植技能。",en:"Builds strong bones.\nImproves farmer skills."};
descriptions["12519"]={cn:"别担心，这鱼又可爱又新鲜。\n提升钓鱼技能。",en:"Don\'t worry: This fish is lovely and fresh.\nImproves fisherman skills."};
descriptions["12520"]={cn:"可爱极了！你只能嫉妒得摆弄下上面的粉色咕咕羽毛！",en:"It\'s so pwitty you might just ruffle Pink Piwis\' feathers with jealousy!"};
descriptions["12521"]={cn:"你并不需要这件手工缝制的外套，不过必须承认牧人在穿衣打扮上确实很有品味。",en:"You don\'t really need this hand-woven jacket, but you\'ve got to admit that Moogrr Tamers have great taste in clothes."};
descriptions["12522"]={cn:"女皇喜欢像个国王...呃不...像个女皇一样到处走走。",en:"Empresses like to impress so pop on this bustier and walk around like a king... urr... or perhaps like a queen."};
descriptions["12523"]={cn:"在不同的环境下，勾引到的回头率也不同。",en:"The rustles from this cape might cause quite a stir depending on the company you\'re in."};
descriptions["12524"]={cn:"哦啦啦！哦啦啦！哦雷雷雷...哦哦！",en:"Ole! Ola! Ole! Oleeeeee... Ow!"};
descriptions["12525"]={cn:"由以坚韧和芬芳而闻名的哞哞草编织而成，女皇披风是当之无愧的杰作！",en:"Woven with Moogrr Grass, which is well known for its sturdiness and its delicate aroma, the Empress Cape is a fine piece of work!"};
descriptions["12526"]={cn:"收集 10 块碎片，组合成商业庇护宝石。",en:"Collect 10 of these fragments to create a Merchant Haven-Gem."};
descriptions["12527"]={cn:"收集 10 块碎片，组合成花园庇护宝石。",en:"Collect 10 of these fragments to create a Garden Haven-Gem."};
descriptions["12528"]={cn:"收集 10 块碎片，组合成制造庇护宝石。",en:"Collect 10 of these fragments to create a Merchant Haven-Gem."};
descriptions["12529"]={cn:"款式别致，舒适合脚。",en:"They\'re chic, and comfortable to boot."};
descriptions["12530"]={cn:"收集 5 块碎片，组合成装饰庇护宝石。",en:"Collect 5 of these fragments to create a Deco Haven-Gem."};
descriptions["12531"]={cn:"专挑敌人背后下手，只要绕到敌人背后，再高的伤害也打得出...！",en:"Used on the backside of an adversary, these boots will allow the wearer to do pretty much whatever they want, actually...!"};
