descriptions["12552"]={cn:"你将会是下一个幸运之星。",en:"A whack from this sword will hit your enemies like a bolt from the blue."};
descriptions["12554"]={cn:"野性绵球的唾液是一种强力的胡椒。谁教你往眼睛里洒的？",en:"Wild Gobball spit is particularly peppery so try to make sure you get it on your plate, and not in your eyes."};
descriptions["12556"]={cn:"献给创生之力的信徒。",en:"For those who believe in the power of Wakfu."};
descriptions["12557"]={cn:"献给创生之力的信徒。",en:"For those who believe in the power of Wakfu."};
