descriptions["12561"]={cn:"献给创生之力的信徒。",en:"For those who believe in the power of Wakfu."};
descriptions["12562"]={cn:"经过精心烹调，这块羊肋排美味多汁，香嫩可口。要掌握好火候，一旦过头，就老得跟破皮靴一样。",en:"Cooked to perfection, this Flank is delicious, succulent, and tender. Cook it too much, however, and it\'s as tough as an old boot."};
descriptions["12563"]={cn:"即便是最熟练的制革师也要竭尽全力才能处理这种皮。",en:"Even the most adept of tanners would have to work very hard to make anything out of this."};
descriptions["12564"]={cn:"看起来，你刷得越猛，它越纠结。",en:"It seems that the more you brush it, the more knotted it gets."};
descriptions["12565"]={cn:"野性绵球会不停地横冲直撞。所以他们的角会磨损也没什么好奇怪的。",en:"Wild Gobballs will butt anything and everything, so it should come as no great surprise that their horns are so worn."};
descriptions["12566"]={cn:"野性绵球都有很深的颜色，从大老远就可以看得一清二楚。",en:"Wild Gobballs have a distinct color which means they can be identified from great distances."};
descriptions["12567"]={cn:"即便是秃子，带着这顶帽子也像植过发一样。",en:"Even baldies will look like they\'ve just got out of bed with this mop on their shiny heads."};
descriptions["12568"]={cn:"让你的双脚舒适温暖。夏天除外。",en:"These boots will keep your feet lovely and warm, even in summer!"};
descriptions["12569"]={cn:"我觉得你再也不可能往护肩里塞更多的东西了。哦？你试过了？",en:"I don\'t think you could stuff any more padding into these epaulettes if you tried! Oh, you have tried."};
descriptions["12570"]={cn:"让腰部温暖舒适，舒缓你的坐姿。",en:"This belt will keep your lumbar region nice and warm, which should soothe that dodgy disk of yours."};
descriptions["12571"]={cn:"盾牌上紧密的卷毛看起来厚实坚硬。可以轻易打乱敌人的如意算盘。",en:"The tight curls on this shield are so thick and healthy they\'ll easily put a crimp on your enemies\' plans."};
descriptions["12572"]={cn:"顺着毛轻轻抚摸它，否则它会反咬你一口。",en:"Stroke these Gobbcards in the direction of the wool, or they\'ll turn around and bite you."};
descriptions["12573"]={cn:"强大的武器，散发着绵球骚味。",en:"An incredibly wild weapon that stinks of Gobball."};
descriptions["12574"]={cn:"不只满足于敲敲打打，始终渴望着撕咬敌人。",en:"Not happy with being banged, this hammer bites and scratches too."};
descriptions["12575"]={cn:"你听说过疯狂牧羊人吗？他养着一大群野性绵球。太奇怪了...！",en:"Have you ever heard the story about the crazy shepherdess who liked to herd herds of Wild Gobballs? It\'s absurd...!"};
descriptions["12576"]={cn:"如果你尝试圈养野性绵球，那么祝你好运...",en:"Good luck using this staff to manage a herd of Wild Gobballs..."};
descriptions["12577"]={cn:"把脑袋靠在肩垫上，安然入睡，醒来却脖颈僵直。",en:"Lay your head on your shoulder, drift gently off to sleep, and end up with a stiff neck."};
descriptions["12578"]={cn:"你完全可以在照看绵球的同时也站在时尚的顶峰。",en:"There\'s no reason why you can\'t look after Gobballs and be the height of fashion at the same time."};
descriptions["12579"]={cn:"自在舒适不紧绷。",en:"This ring will keep your finger as snug as a bug in a rug."};
descriptions["12580"]={cn:"能召集所有的绵球。",en:"This breastplate brings all the Gobballs to the yard."};
descriptions["12581"]={cn:"舒适贴身。",en:"A comforting woolen amulet."};
descriptions["12582"]={cn:"可以用作洗衣板，十分便利。",en:"When you\'re not wearing this cape, you can use it as a very effective scouring pad."};
descriptions["12583"]={cn:"难以驾驭。但是拗成两段，你会觉得它十分有用。",en:"This baguette may be difficult to tame, but once you\'ve broken it, you\'ll find it incredibly useful."};
descriptions["12584"]={cn:"够咸了，不要再放盐了。",en:"All peppered up, so don\'t push it with the salt."};
descriptions["12585"]={cn:"让人印象深刻的犄角，特别是当它插进你的屁股的时候。",en:"This horn is pretty impressive, especially when it\'s stuck deep into your left buttock."};
descriptions["12586"]={cn:"造型独特的头盔，让其他冒险者像绵绵一样在你周围聚集。",en:"This impressively-built helmet will cause adventurers to come flocking around you like Gobblies. Oh, wait..."};
descriptions["12587"]={cn:"不要被柔软的绒毛欺骗了，这件胸甲切大石如切黄油。而且并不能保证使用者的人身安全。",en:"Don\'t be fooled by the softness of the wool, this breastplate will cut rocks like butter. It doesn\'t guarantee the safety of its wearer, however."};
descriptions["12588"]={cn:"纪念你与神圣绵球的战斗。",en:"This amulet is a fine souvenir of your battle with Gobbsage."};
descriptions["12589"]={cn:"厚实的披风，让你温暖备至！",en:"This incredibly thick coat will keep you... incredibly warm!"};
descriptions["12590"]={cn:"如果你看到有人穿着这对护肩攻击你，看在幸运猫的份上，马上转身逃跑吧！",en:"If you see someone charging towards you wearing these epaulettes, then for Eca\'s sake run as fast as you can in the other direction!"};
descriptions["12591"]={cn:"挖掘一切零零碎碎。",en:"This shovel is useful for unearthing all kinds of bits and pieces."};
descriptions["12592"]={cn:"是的，它打人很痛！",en:"And yes, it really hurts!"};
descriptions["12593"]={cn:"点击两下来把整组古代资源转换成新的资源。古代资源需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["12594"]={cn:"铃铛一响，迅速冷冻任何食物。",en:"A little tinkle and you\'ll be able to freeze any food."};
descriptions["12595"]={cn:"可以绣在各种时装上的纽扣。",en:"Buttons can be sewn onto various garments."};
descriptions["12596"]={cn:"主教布道的时候可以偷偷打个瞌睡，没有一个僧侣会告诉你这个小窍门的。",en:"The monks might not tell you this but it\'s very useful for taking a snooze during sermons."};
descriptions["12597"]={cn:"缓解双脚疲劳，减少腿部赘肉。简直就是为你专门设计的。",en:"These slippers soothe tired feet and pre-emptively treat verrucas. Looks like they\'ve got their work cut out with you."};
descriptions["12598"]={cn:"指环上可能还留有口水。显然，这是因为在修道院里人们动不动就亲吻对方的戒指来打招呼的缘故。",en:"It\'s possible that this ring has still got some saliva on it. Apparently, it\'s customary in the monastery for people to kiss one another\'s rings as a way of saying hello."};
descriptions["12599"]={cn:"男女通用。在宗教仪式上穿着。",en:"This tunic, which is often worn during religious ceremonies, suits men as well as women."};
descriptions["12600"]={cn:"所谓的赐福仪式就是...拿权杖敲一下脑袋。务必掌握好轻重！",en:"Give someone your blessing by bashing them on the head."};
descriptions["12601"]={cn:"这根手杖刚刚好，帮助你健步如飞。",en:"This cane is just as good at tripping people up as it is at helping you to walk."};
descriptions["12602"]={cn:"我是僧侣的舅舅！这个戒指可是当世最强的。",en:"Well, I\'ll be a monk\'s uncle! This ring is second to nun."};
descriptions["12603"]={cn:"这鞋子太破旧了，你看大脚趾头都露在外面，你介意吗？不介意吧。",en:"These slippers are so old and worn that you can see your enormous big toe sticking out of the end.\nMind you, that\'s not difficult, is it?"};
descriptions["12604"]={cn:"净化罪恶的敌人。",en:"Instantly absolves the sins of your enemies."};
descriptions["12605"]={cn:"很难说到底有多少神职人员系着它。据说最早用来保证他们没办法频繁上床脱裤子。",en:"It\'s hard to tell how many clergyman actually wear this belt, but it\'s supposed to help hold up your trousers."};
descriptions["12606"]={cn:"用于在教堂里敲钟，当然也可以敲敌人的脑袋。",en:"This hammer can be used to ring church bells, or the heads of your enemies."};
descriptions["12607"]={cn:"不要妄想着靠有人来免费填满它。你要知道，别人又不是傻瓜！",en:"Just don\'t expect anyone to fill it up for free. People aren\'t idiots, you know!"};
descriptions["12608"]={cn:"现在你知道他们把剃下的头发藏在哪里了。",en:"Now you know where they put the hair from their tonsures."};
descriptions["12609"]={cn:"在奶牛们回家之前，你会忍不住想吃掉这块奶酪。",en:"You\'ll be wanting to eat this cheese until the cows come home."};
descriptions["12610"]={cn:"我那副约翰·列蒙的眼镜在哪儿？",en:"Now, where are my Jon Lemon glasses?"};
descriptions["12611"]={cn:"修道院里的僧侣们会为了这套卡牌抢破头。",en:"These cards are highly regarded by the monks that collect them in the monastery."};
descriptions["12613"]={cn:"牧师们团结的象征。",en:"This sword looks like it might cause almighty pain but it unites the clergymen all the same."};
descriptions["12615"]={cn:"幽灵专用。",en:"This prism has a ghostly beauty."};
descriptions["12616"]={cn:"这种清灵的栖息能使最死寂的伙伴也复苏过来，他们绝不会再次死去！",en:"This invigorating gust will awaken even the deadest of your comrades.\nThey\'ll be up and ready to die again in no time!"};
descriptions["12617"]={cn:"你觉得背后一凉。",en:"The temperature drops with this icy veil over your shoulders."};
descriptions["12618"]={cn:"哦天啊！姐妹，你美极了！",en:"Holy moly! Sister, you are looking goooood!"};
descriptions["12619"]={cn:"皮肤被冻得出血。",en:"It\'ll freeze your skin until it bleeds!"};
descriptions["12620"]={cn:"穿过你的心脏（放心不会死！）。",en:"Cross your heart (but don\'t hope to die!)."};
descriptions["12621"]={cn:"穿过你的心脏（放心不会死！）。",en:"Cross your heart (but don\'t hope to die!)."};
descriptions["12622"]={cn:"穿上是腰带，脱下来就是抹布。",en:"When you take this off, you can use it to protect the table from nasty stains."};
descriptions["12623"]={cn:"你看上去像极了死神，而且更恐怖。",en:"Now you look like the Grim Reaper, but scarier."};
descriptions["12624"]={cn:"它能够清理到最脏的角落。",en:"It gets deep into the dirtiest corners."};
descriptions["12625"]={cn:"放下屠刀，立地成佛。",en:"It will forgive your fallen opponents immediately."};
descriptions["12626"]={cn:"涂满了奶油，气味芬芳。",en:"These cream-filled puff pastries smell delicious."};
descriptions["12627"]={cn:"每个人都需要空间来装一点私人物品，特别是修女。",en:"Everyone needs a pouch for their private things, especially nuns."};
descriptions["12628"]={cn:"轻轻一挥，敌人成灰。",en:"You\'ll sort your enemies out in one clear sweep with this brush."};
descriptions["12629"]={cn:"不管什么场合，女仆都是最棒的！",en:"This should come in handy in all sorts of situations!"};
descriptions["12630"]={cn:"你知道吗，你现在看起来就像是刚从下水道爬出来一样。",en:"You look like you just crawled out of a sewer, you know."};
descriptions["12631"]={cn:"当心你的手指！啊，已经迟了...",en:"Watch where you put that finger! Oops, too late..."};
descriptions["12632"]={cn:"现在你知道为什么路上那些幸运猫在你经过的时候始终在吞口水了。",en:"Now you know why those Ecaflips were licking their lips when you walked past them a moment ago."};
descriptions["12633"]={cn:"献给创生之力的信徒。",en:"For those who believe in the power of Wakfu."};
descriptions["12634"]={cn:"献给创生之力的信徒。",en:"For those who believe in the power of Wakfu."};
descriptions["12635"]={cn:"献给创生之力的信徒。",en:"For those who believe in the power of Wakfu."};
descriptions["12636"]={cn:"闻到老鼠味道了？",en:"Smell a rat...? Oh..."};
descriptions["12637"]={cn:"上一个主人弄丢了这把魔杖，因为他后来一个手指都不剩了。",en:"Apparently this wand\'s last owner dropped it because he didn\'t have any fingers left."};
descriptions["12638"]={cn:"脏兮兮的项链，说不定会为你带来疾病。别被吓到了！",en:"This dirty necklace might just give you some nasty diseases. Don\'t get pooped out!"};
descriptions["12639"]={cn:"坚硬锋利，能刺穿任何皮肤。",en:"This hair is very rough and sharp against the skin."};
descriptions["12640"]={cn:"被老鼠偷走的奶酪，上面还留着几根鼠毛。",en:"This lump of strong-smelling cheese has been nibbled\nand is covered in hair."};
descriptions["12641"]={cn:"由鼠毛制成。",en:"This string is made entirely from woven rat hair."};
descriptions["12642"]={cn:"混合了蔬菜和死老鼠的菜式！",en:"A subtle blend of summer vegetables and old rats!"};
descriptions["12643"]={cn:"你也许根本不想背上它。但是它很好用，熏人的臭气能让小偷滚得远远的。",en:"The stench coming off it acts as an effective deterrent for would-be thieves."};
descriptions["12645"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["12646"]={cn:"我为人人，人人为...那个骑士在搞什么飞机！",en:"One for all, and all for... What in the World is that Iop doing?!"};
descriptions["12647"]={cn:"从现在的样子来看，这只咕咕恶贯满盈，死期已至。",en:"Given the way it looks now, this Googoo\'s devious days are over!"};
descriptions["12648"]={cn:"点击两下来把旧物品转换成相同类型的新物品。",en:"Double-click to transform your old item into a new one of the same type."};
