descriptions["12669"]={cn:"由上等的绿啾啾羽毛所装饰，征服这个城市的夜晚吧！",en:"Adorned with the finest finery of a Green Piwi, you\'re ready for a night on the town!"};
descriptions["12670"]={cn:"采摘果实是个苦差事。这条头巾能不能让你舒服点呢？",en:"The laborious chore of picking plants isn\'t enough to make you Api. Does this hood help any?"};
descriptions["12671"]={cn:"塞得下宝藏猎人的蜂窝的超大帽子。扑灭害虫的专用工具。",en:"A great big helmet that could even hide an Enutrof\'s beehive. Ideal headwear for fixing up some grub."};
descriptions["12672"]={cn:"哦啦啦！真潇洒！",en:"Ooh la la! C\'est chic!"};
descriptions["12673"]={cn:"有什么东西比面粉袋更性感？当然只有这件农夫衬衣了！",en:"What could be sexier than a holey flour sack? Why, this Farmer Shirt, of course!"};
descriptions["12674"]={cn:"说实话，穿着它可别想去务农。",en:"Let\'s be honest, you\'re hardly going to go harvesting in this attire."};
descriptions["12675"]={cn:"歌里唱得好，钻石是女性之友。好吧，如果你买不起钻石，起码你还有...这件独特的披风。",en:"Diamonds are a girl\'s best friend, or so the song goes. Well, if you can\'t get diamonds, there\'s always this... peculiar cape."};
descriptions["12676"]={cn:"穿起来，在田野里玩一整天！",en:"You\'ll have a field day playing around in this set."};
descriptions["12677"]={cn:"价值三袋大麦粉。好吧，其实不是很多。但是想想你可以做多少麦粉小饼吧！",en:"This cape is worth three sacks of barley flour. Alright, it\'s not very much, but just think of all the Tortikuri you could have made!"};
descriptions["12678"]={cn:"无论是沙尘暴还是溅到了苹朵沙司，给你全方位的防护。",en:"These epaulettes will protect you from bad weather, dust and Apisauce splashbacks."};
descriptions["12679"]={cn:"天然纤维制成，洒满淀粉。",en:"Woven from natural fiber and softened with starch."};
descriptions["12680"]={cn:"这双靴子真的源自世界时尚之都？！",en:"Are these boots really meant to be from the World capital of fashion?!"};
descriptions["12681"]={cn:"法尔的鞋子的复制品，连洞洞都一样！",en:"These shoes are exact replicas of Farle\'s shoes; they even have the same holes!"};
descriptions["12682"]={cn:"鞋底粘着一些糖浆，所以如果黏住了一大堆你刚见过的东西，不要觉得惊讶。",en:"The sole of these shoes is stuck on with Glucosyrup so don\'t be surprised if you harvest everything you walk on!"};
descriptions["12683"]={cn:"千年之前到现在的沧海桑田尽收眼底。\n混乱与复兴的见证。",en:"This headgear represents the passage from the Dofus Era to the Wakfu Era.\nIt marks chaos and revival."};
descriptions["12684"]={cn:"少年不识愁，与天试比高。\n脱我旧时装，着我豆芙袍。结伴去远征，同行皆英豪。",en:"You always dreamt of being part of the Brotherhood of Tofu.\nWell, with this cloak you can make your own brotherhood and head off on an adventure all together!"};
descriptions["12685"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few drops should suffice."};
descriptions["12686"]={cn:"你可以在下列兑奖机中兑换奖励:喵外婆小屋，绵球草原，豆芙屋，变异虫巢穴。",en:"Use the following machines to exchange your tokens for fantastic rewards: Bow Meow, Gobball, Tofu, Larva."};
