descriptions["12750"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["12751"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["12752"]={cn:"十分结实，难以解开。即便是最锋利的宝剑也无法切断。",en:"This strap is so resistant that you\'ll find it difficult to take off, even with your most powerful sword."};
descriptions["12757"]={cn:"教会你在大雨倾盆的时候，用不可模仿的经典姿势撑起雨伞。",en:"This scroll will teach you the ancient and inimitable art of protecting yourself against the rain when it\'s lashing down."};
descriptions["12758"]={cn:"教会你在大雨倾盆的时候，用不可模仿的经典姿势撑起雨伞。",en:"This scroll will teach you the ancient and inimitable art of protecting yourself against the rain when it\'s lashing down."};
descriptions["12759"]={cn:"教会你在大雨倾盆的时候，用不可模仿的经典姿势撑起雨伞。",en:"This scroll will teach you the ancient and inimitable art of protecting yourself against the rain when it\'s lashing down."};
descriptions["12767"]={cn:"现在你可以戴着铃铛攻击敌人了！",en:"Now you can attack your enemies with bells on!"};
descriptions["12768"]={cn:"狼牙深深嵌入你的手指！",en:"It\'ll sink its fangs into your finger!"};
descriptions["12769"]={cn:"很不错的狩猎战利品！",en:"A well-earned hunting trophy!"};
descriptions["12770"]={cn:"傲然立于狼群之首！",en:"Stand tall and proud in this headgear!"};
descriptions["12774"]={cn:"前往地下城门口的兑奖机处兑换酷炫的奖励。",en:"Use the machine across from the dungeon to exchange your tokens for fantastic rewards."};
descriptions["12776"]={cn:"披风的热度让你挥汗如雨。",en:"The heat from this cape will ensure that you develop a constant coat of sweat and perpetual body odor."};
descriptions["12777"]={cn:"即便是最干燥的手，戴上这只戒指后也能变得红润有光泽。",en:"Even the driest of hands will get all hot and sweaty once this radiant ring is popped onto one of their fingers."};
descriptions["12779"]={cn:"让你的身体温暖一整天。",en:"This breastplate will keep your torso warm all day long."};
descriptions["12780"]={cn:"这条腰带感觉像电热毯...区别在于它在你的腰上。",en:"This belt is like an electric blanket... except it\'s around your waist."};
descriptions["12784"]={cn:"双手牢牢地抓住这柄法杖，顿时感觉精神一震，准备行动！",en:"If you take hold of this staff firmly with both hands it\'ll seem to come to life and stiffen, ready for action!"};
descriptions["12785"]={cn:"丑陋或是时尚！由你决定！",en:"Ugly or fashionable? You decide!"};
descriptions["12786"]={cn:"在黑暗中行走而不至于迷路？请用火把！",en:"Need to find your way through dark places without getting utterly lost? Then you need this torch!"};
descriptions["12788"]={cn:"小心点，别让匕首在你手里爆炸了！",en:"Watch out that this dagger doesn\'t explode in your hands!"};
descriptions["12789"]={cn:"戴上手铐意味着你的双手失去自由，但是你还是能用脚...和头！",en:"Wearing this bracelet might mean that your hands are out of action but you can still use your feet... and your head!"};
descriptions["12790"]={cn:"保护你的头部免受坠落之物的伤害。你可不知道铁砧会掉在哪儿！",en:"This hat will protect your head from any falling objects whilst you\'re here. You never know when an anvil might fall out of nowhere!"};
descriptions["12791"]={cn:"靴子的特制内衬，提供良好的缓冲性能，脚底再也不会起泡。",en:"These boots have special insoles that prevent rubbing and blisters - your feet are sure to be as pleased as punch... ur... kick."};
descriptions["12792"]={cn:"这件外套很好看，其实并不会提供多好的防护。那么，对于野外冒险来说是好看还是防护更重要呢...？",en:"This jacket won\'t protect you too well, but it certainly looks good. Now, which is more important for wild adventures...?"};
descriptions["12794"]={cn:"有可能会伤到你的头骨。但是你是从斯雷克那里得到的...你还能指望些什么？",en:"It might crush your skull, but you got it from the Schneks - what did you expect?"};
descriptions["12795"]={cn:"吸水性强，紧紧贴住你的皮肤。",en:"This spongy cloak will stick to your skin like proverbial feces to a blanket."};
descriptions["12796"]={cn:"斯雷克护膝让你远离受伤烦恼...湿软的内衬，足以抵抗任何冲击。",en:"You needn\'t worry about getting attacked with these knee pads on - they\'re squidgy enough to cushion the blow."};
descriptions["12797"]={cn:"弹力极强的手镯，适合任何手腕...甚至是你的，肥仔！",en:"This elastic bracelet will fit around any wrist... even yours!"};
descriptions["12798"]={cn:"只要能使用正确，你就能攻敌人于不备。",en:"If you play these cards right you could really hurt an enemy when they\'re least expecting it."};
descriptions["12799"]={cn:"伸缩自如，适用于任何一根手指。",en:"This ring is so elastic it will adapt its size to any finger you choose to wear it on."};
descriptions["12800"]={cn:"甩出这条鞭子，敌人像蠕虫一样退却。",en:"Whip this out and watch your adversaries squirm!"};
descriptions["12801"]={cn:"你该休息下，为什么不在盾牌后面躲一会儿...？",en:"You deserve a break, so why not just hide behind this schnexy schield...?"};
descriptions["12802"]={cn:"能承受一切赘肉！",en:"This belt will hold in all that excess weight!"};
descriptions["12803"]={cn:"前任主人往上面抹了不少润滑油。即便是最肥的脸也能塞进去。让大家看看你的斯雷克面具吧！",en:"This mask is so well-lubricated by its previous owner that even the fattest face can be crammed in. Show us your Schnek\'s face!"};
descriptions["12804"]={cn:"斯雷克女皇的子嗣之一。",en:"The Queen Schnek has passed on one of her many offspring."};
descriptions["12806"]={cn:"很难看懂，似乎指向某段古老的墙壁...",en:"You can barely read it, but it seems to indicate some kind of big old wall..."};
descriptions["12807"]={cn:"巴里写给克劳德的信，真诚溢于言表。",en:"A heartfelt letter from Barry to Claude."};
descriptions["12808"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few drops should suffice."};
descriptions["12809"]={cn:"痒死你！",en:"This hair will literally tickle you to death!"};
descriptions["12810"]={cn:"极度缺乏阳光照射和维他命。",en:"This skin is very seriously lacking in sunlight and vitamins."};
descriptions["12811"]={cn:"点击两下来把整组古代资源转换成新的资源。古代资源需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["12812"]={cn:"点击两下来把整组古代资源转换成新的资源。古代资源需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["12813"]={cn:"只要一滴就能让你卧床不起。",en:"Just one drop of this blood could make you ill for all eternity."};
descriptions["12814"]={cn:"点击两下来把整组古代资源转换成新的资源。古代资源需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["12815"]={cn:"防水功效出众，是蝙蝠球风雨无阻的重要原因。",en:"Borbats don\'t care about bad weather. These wings are as waterproof as waterproof can be!"};
descriptions["12816"]={cn:"穿戴起来可能有点花时间，但是值得。这可是由纯正吸血蝙蝠皮制成的！",en:"It might mess you around a bit, but it\'s made of genuine vampiric Borbat leather!"};
descriptions["12817"]={cn:"千里之行，始于足下。",en:"So you can always set off on the right fut."};
descriptions["12818"]={cn:"戴上它，远离小肚腩的烦恼！",en:"If you thought gaining a few inches around the middle was bad, try a whole fut!"};
descriptions["12819"]={cn:"紧致的胸甲，给你超级英雄般的身材！",en:"This ultra-tight breastplate will give you super-hero abs!"};
descriptions["12820"]={cn:"哦，究竟谁才是漂亮的小猫？",en:"Awww, who\'s a pwiddy puddy cat?!"};
descriptions["12821"]={cn:"你看起来棒极了！",en:"Why, you look just purrrrfect!"};
descriptions["12822"]={cn:"现在你可以学习怎样迈猫步了！",en:"Now you can learn how to walk the catwalk properly!"};
descriptions["12823"]={cn:"据说拍打喵毛能带来好运。别穿出去！",en:"They say that stroking your tuft can bring good luck. Don\'t wear it out, now!"};
descriptions["12825"]={cn:"你可以试着躲藏，但是一点用都没有...所有人都听得到你脖子上铃铛的响声。",en:"You can try to hide but there\'s not really any point... everyone will hear you pouncing around with this bell hanging around your neck."};
descriptions["12826"]={cn:"让你像小野猫一样敏捷灵动。",en:"This staff will make you as agile as a cat in battle."};
descriptions["12827"]={cn:"轻轻一挥，灰尘扫光光。",en:"Swish this feather around a bit in your Haven Bag, and bang: The dust is gone!"};
descriptions["12828"]={cn:"如果你喜欢这顶头盔，那是因为在内心深处，你跟佐拉一样烦人。",en:"If you like wearing this hat, it\'s because deep down you\'re just as annoying as Zora."};
descriptions["12829"]={cn:"为豆芙庆典期间的孩子们定制。",en:"This amulet is made for children during the Tofu ceremony."};
descriptions["12830"]={cn:"麻烦转告你的脚趾，它们的好运来了...这双靴子舒适极了！",en:"Tell your tootsies it\'s their lucky day - these boots are as comfy as comfy could be!"};
descriptions["12831"]={cn:"保护你的双手免受任性的豆芙啄咬。",en:"This glove protects your hands from those capricious Tofu pecks."};
descriptions["12832"]={cn:"当你穿上这件黄色的豆芙短衣，阳光会从你不知道的地方照耀过来！",en:"The sun will shine out of places you didn\'t know existed when you don this yellow Tofu tunic!"};
descriptions["12833"]={cn:"柔软的披风，可以用来当毯子。睡个好觉吧...晚安好梦！",en:"This cloak makes a great blanky. Cozy on down for the night... Sweet dreams!"};
descriptions["12835"]={cn:"柔软舒适，带着这块盾牌，最坚定的冒险者也忍不住在太阳底下伸个懒腰。",en:"This shield is so soft and snuggly that it\'ll make even the toughest adventurer want to curl up and snooze in the sun."};
descriptions["12836"]={cn:"眯着它的双眼，踮着它的脚尖，守着它的爱恋，一转眼却又看不见。",en:"Fuzzy-wuzzy are these cards, these cards are fuzzy-wuzzy... Played correctly against an enemy you could make them quite muzzy."};
descriptions["12855"]={cn:"只是看一眼就能让人胆寒。",en:"Simply looking at this axe will make you complete lose your head."};
descriptions["12856"]={cn:"可以当雨具用！虽然不太时尚，但是当天气寒冷的时候，你会庆幸你拥有它。",en:"It\'s the return of the mac! It might not be very fashionable but when it gets a bit chilly you\'ll be glad you\'ve got this Caghoule to hand."};
descriptions["12857"]={cn:"起码从颈部以上来看，你漂亮得像画中人。",en:"Now you\'re as pretty as a picture, from your head down to your Ghoulie, at least."};
descriptions["12859"]={cn:"无法遏制住击败敌人的迫切欲望...",en:"The Hotty will give you a burning desire to knock out your enemies... as if you didn\'t want to already!"};
descriptions["12860"]={cn:"和皮肤接触时，温度升高！",en:"When in contact with skin, this ring gets really hot!"};
descriptions["12861"]={cn:"从墓穴中挖出，带着刺骨的寒冷。",en:"This ring was found in a cemetery and exudes an aura that will make your blood run cold."};
descriptions["12862"]={cn:"从坟墓里一下又一下击打着地面。",en:"When they said this hammer was all gravey, you didn\'t realize it felt most at home in a cemetery."};
descriptions["12863"]={cn:"嗒嗒嗒嗒！",en:"Clickety clack, clackety click!"};
descriptions["12864"]={cn:"小心，否则它会活吞了你！",en:"Watch out or it will eat you alive!"};
descriptions["12865"]={cn:"虽然已经被扯成破布，但是依然很有用。",en:"Although this breastplate is in tatters, it\'s still reasonably useful."};
descriptions["12866"]={cn:"异域风味的香肠，十分美味！",en:"This exotic-a sausage-a is just magnifico!"};
descriptions["12867"]={cn:"缚灵村特产，很恶心。可是你已经饥不择食了！",en:"This Forfut Village specialty is really, really gross. When you\'re hungry, though, you\'ll eat anything!"};
descriptions["12872"]={cn:"点击两下来把整组古代资源转换成新的资源。古代资源需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["12873"]={cn:"看见这种暗紫色的染料就让你想起吸血公爵，还有他冲澡的时候老唱的那首歌“吸吸吸吸血血血血...”或者类似的调子...",en:"A deep, purple dye to remind you of Vampyro and that song he always sings in the shower: \"Clooooooak in the waaaaater...\" or something like that..."};
descriptions["12878"]={cn:"下面究竟埋着谁？",en:"Is there really someone buried underneath there?"};
descriptions["12880"]={cn:"放出红外射线，治愈各种肌肉酸痛。",en:"These Heaterettes offer a deep-heat effect that soothes all kinds of muscle pain."};
descriptions["12881"]={cn:"即便是已死之人，也能杀给你看。",en:"They say that this hammer can kill dead people a second time over."};
descriptions["12887"]={cn:"它们不从脖子而是从肩膀吸血。",en:"Instead of going for the neck, these epaulettes suck blood from the shoulders."};
descriptions["12888"]={cn:"穿上这件胸甲后你觉得精疲力尽...它能将你的生命能量吸收殆尽。",en:"It\'s normal to feel exhausted after wearing this breastplate...\nIt sucks the life right out of you."};
descriptions["12889"]={cn:"很明显有个穿着紧身斗篷的牙尖嘴利的家伙把这件披风卖给了城堡的主人。最终，他发现这把弓一无是处。",en:"Apparently some smooth-talking dude in a dodgy cape sold this bow to the castle\'s owner, who ended up never really finding a use for it."};
descriptions["12890"]={cn:"看起来幽暗阴森，能为你遮挡阳光...总比在衣服上涂满防晒霜好多了。",en:"It might seem a bit shady but this amulet will protect you from sunburn... \nHey, it\'s a lot cooler than whapping coats of colored sunblock on your face!"};
descriptions["12891"]={cn:"谁说敢吸血鬼很烂？这款有型的手腕证明他们对于时尚的品味。",en:"Whoever said Vampyres suck? This stylish bracelet proves that they have a real eye for fashion."};
descriptions["12893"]={cn:"太重了，随时都会摔倒。",en:"Just the clumps for when you\'re down in the dumps."};
descriptions["12894"]={cn:"像你这样的小恶魔逛街的时候总会随身带一只德古拉达包包！",en:"Little devils like you wouldn\'t be seen dead without their Vamprada bag!"};
descriptions["12895"]={cn:"它需要水...水！\n也许还要点血。",en:"It needs water... WATER!\nAnd maybe a little bit of blood."};
descriptions["12896"]={cn:"暮色降临之时，用这柄魔杖戳瞎敌人的眼睛。在新月升起之前，他们会变成僵尸，自由行动。",en:"At twilight, you can use this wand to fork your enemies\' eyes out. By the time the new moon appears, they\'ll be doing it of their own accord."};
descriptions["12903"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
