descriptions["13058"]={cn:"古墓自助游必备。",en:"For narcoleptics and tomb raiders."};
descriptions["13093"]={cn:"没有必要为塔德波尔树浇水。它会自动生根发芽，慢慢成长为参天大树。",en:"No need to drown this cutting; it\'ll wriggle its way towards water all by itself before growing into a magnificent tree."};
descriptions["13094"]={cn:"跟呆呱脑壳一样硬。要切木片下来要花不少功夫。",en:"This wood is almost as thick as an Oafish Toad.\nYou\'ll need a lot of patience to cut any more."};
descriptions["13095"]={cn:"这种枝条非常适合种植在萨弗基亚的潮湿土壤。",en:"This cutting takes well when planted in Sufokia soil."};
descriptions["13096"]={cn:"在萨弗基亚很常见的木材，但是在十二世界却非常昂贵。因为这种木材的硬度和柔韧度都无与伦比。",en:"The wood from this common Sufokia tree is highly prized in the World of Twelve for its unrivaled strength and suppleness."};
descriptions["13097"]={cn:"听过伐木工李安纳在酒吧的故事吗？他想要的就是这种藤。",en:"Heard the one about the liana who walks into a bar? He just wanted some vine."};
descriptions["13098"]={cn:"从树根到树杈都结着冰，想要加工它你得鼓起勇气，手指头结了冰会很脆的。",en:"This wood is frozen from root to branch. It requires a certain amount of courage to work with it, since frostbitten fingers are a definite hazard."};
descriptions["13099"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["13100"]={cn:"没有人知道在这么冷的地方，树是怎么生长的。",en:"Amazing how this cutting manages to grow up through its chilly shell in an environment as icy as Frigost\'s!"};
