descriptions["13107"]={cn:"搭配任何膳食都十分完美。更多时候被当做小食和食盐一起上桌。",en:"These tasty nuts go well with almost any meal, but are more often served up as nibbles with a sprinkle of Verbala Salt."};
descriptions["13108"]={cn:"夏季点心的大众之选。",en:"A popular choice for summery snacks."};
descriptions["13109"]={cn:"紫杉树生长周期很长，所以尽早种吧！",en:"Yew grows relatively slowly, so the sooner you plant it the better!"};
descriptions["13110"]={cn:"你知道制造弓弩和其他坚固又有弹性的武器的最好材料吗？是的，就是紫杉木...",en:"Do you want to know what\'s great for making bows and other sturdy, flexible weapons? Yes? I knew Yew Wood..."};
descriptions["13111"]={cn:"具有化腐朽为神奇的功效...",en:"If it were a case of life or death... Yew wood, wouldn\'t you!"};
