descriptions["13138"]={cn:"幸运兔脚在缚灵村一点用也没有！试试这些 100% 纯蝙蝠纤维制成的护符！",en:"In Forfut Village, lucky Wodent feet won\'t get you anywhere! Try one of these 100% organic Borbat-fiber amulets instead."};
descriptions["13139"]={cn:"它们的味道可能相似，但这些恶臭菌孢子可不能与宝藏猎人的疣搞混。",en:"They may taste similar, but these Funkus Spores are not to be confused with Enutrof verruca powder."};
descriptions["13140"]={cn:"名字听起来很酷。但是不要被耍了...它能造成恶心以及恶臭。",en:"The name of this mushroom makes it sound pretty cool. But don\'t be fooled - the nausea it causes and its funky smell prove that it really isn\'t cool at all."};
descriptions["13141"]={cn:"点击两下来把整组古代资源转换成新的资源。古代资源需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["13142"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["13143"]={cn:"因为外观清丽，雪绒花广受欢迎。",en:"The magnificent flower that grows from this seed is very popular for its outstanding beauty."};
descriptions["13144"]={cn:"雪绒花，代表爱情和纯洁。\n婚礼的那天，为你的终生伴侣戴上一朵。",en:"Edelweiss represents love and purity.\nIt\'s traditional to give a sprig to your spouse-to-be on your wedding day."};
descriptions["13145"]={cn:"也被称作“冬日之星”。它闪烁着温暖的红光，为试图穿越雪原的冒险者引导方向。",en:"This flower is also known as the \'winter star.\' Glowing with a warm light, it acts as a guide for adventurers crossing snowy plains."};
descriptions["13146"]={cn:"有的人使用棉花纤维来塞枕头，希望能睡得实在，做个好梦。",en:"Some people use Cotton fibers to stuff their pillows, hoping it\'ll help them get some cotton-picking sleep."};
descriptions["13147"]={cn:"由著名的棉花协会引进的品种。在那以后，这种开花植物生长旺盛。能工巧匠争相收集它所生产的棉纱。",en:"Cotton was introduced to nature by the famous Cotton Committee some time ago. The flowering plant has thrived ever since, and craftsmen can\'t get enough of the Spun Cotton it produces."};
descriptions["13148"]={cn:"比一般的棉花粗糙。但是对于工匠而言依然很有价值。",en:"Malted Cotton is rougher than the normal stuff, but that doesn\'t make it any less valuable for craftsmen."};
descriptions["13149"]={cn:"确保在使用前把蘑菇洗干净...它的褶子之间的洞大得可以住进一窝鼹鼠了。",en:"Make sure you wash and double-wash this mushroom before you use it - there\'s enough earth stuck in its gills to house a colony of moles."};
descriptions["13150"]={cn:"这种子在斯拉姆神域能茁壮成长",en:"This seed takes well when planted in Srambad soil."};
descriptions["13151"]={cn:"三叶株是一种有效的防腐剂。如果你吃下去，它会让你昏迷一会儿。",en:"The Clobbver is an effective antiseptic. If you eat it, it will knock you out for a little while."};
descriptions["13152"]={cn:"四叶株鬼鬼祟祟的。它耐心的等待，找准时机让你失去理智。",en:"The Clowver is sneaky. It waits patiently for just the wrong moment to takes its effect and make you take leave of your senses."};
descriptions["13153"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["13159"]={cn:"太阳亚麻... 大概永远用不到！",en:"Sun Flax... now there\'s something we\'ll never need!"};
descriptions["13162"]={cn:"这种子能在喱维萨茁壮成长。",en:"This seed takes well when planted in Costa del Sol soil."};
descriptions["13163"]={cn:"苦中作乐。",en:"Makoffee to die for!"};
descriptions["13164"]={cn:"金核桃仁是财富和梦想的象征。",en:"Pure Arabraca is a measure of wealth and dreams."};
descriptions["13165"]={cn:"豌豆射手的子弹。一大波僵尸接近中。",en:"These seeds are best known for their use as pea-shooter ammo."};
descriptions["13166"]={cn:"据说西瓜会导致某种鸵鸟的灭绝，这种鸵鸟大半生的时间在灌木丛里睡觉。",en:"They say that Watermelons led to the demise of a certain breed of Strich which spent all its time sleeping in the bushes."};
descriptions["13167"]={cn:"食欲大开。",en:"This Watermelon will greatly increase your appetite."};
descriptions["13168"]={cn:"复仇的滋味更甜了。",en:"With this corn revenge will taste even sweeter."};
descriptions["13169"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["13170"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["13171"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["13172"]={cn:"埋下这颗种子，豆茎长得直插云霄...！好吧，也许没有那么高...",en:"Plant this seed to create a beanstalk as tall as the sky...! OK, maybe not that tall..."};
descriptions["13174"]={cn:"小小的种子居然能长出壮实的草莓株，结满了可口的果实。",en:"It\'s hard to believe that this tiny seed will give life to a robust strawberry plant, laden with delicious fruit."};
descriptions["13176"]={cn:"摆出你贵族的架势，来尝尝这种葡萄。如果雇人喂食，效果更佳。",en:"Nibble these at all social events for a classic, aristocratic look. It works even better if you employ someone to pluck them and feed them to you."};
descriptions["13177"]={cn:"献给神的贡品。",en:"The gods\' snack of choice."};
descriptions["13178"]={cn:"提升创造力。骑士们拥有丰富想象力的原因就是因为他们整天都戴着这种水晶护符！",en:"They say that this stone enhances creativity. That\'s probably why Iops have such a vivid imagination - they wear this amethyst all the time!"};
descriptions["13180"]={cn:"珊瑚活着的时候充满了光泽，然而现在已不再那么亮丽了。",en:"Once living and full of splendor, it\'s now lost much of its luster."};
descriptions["13181"]={cn:"如此罕见保存完好的石头，一定会有大用处。",en:"This remarkably well-preserved stone can probably be used to make powerful objects."};
descriptions["13182"]={cn:"即便是在史蒂芬冰山，塔罗迪姆矿也是十分稀有的，它之所以深受大众的喜爱与它本身极为高质量的耐用度是脱不了关系的，更可贵的是它依然有很多不为人知的优点还未被发掘，所以它注定价值连城。",en:"Taroudium is a very rare crystal and Styffen Chillberg is no slouch at marketing it. It\'s extremely popular because it\'s highly durable and possesses many as yet unknown virtues. It\'s worth its weight in kamas!"};
descriptions["13183"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["13184"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["13185"]={cn:"找到这种矿石的最简单方法就是跟随矿道另一端的亮光。",en:"If you\'re having trouble mining this ore just look for the light at the end of the tunnel."};
descriptions["13188"]={cn:"它梦想着生出双脚，爬上陆地行走，但是它的鱼鳍实在太短了。",en:"The Maskerel longs to change its mask like its land-living brothers, but its fins are just too short."};
descriptions["13189"]={cn:"时不时飞出水面。",en:"It believed it could touch the sky."};
descriptions["13190"]={cn:"新手会把小龙虾和虾搞混。任何一个美食家都会告诉你小龙虾比普通的虾个头大得多，也更加美味。",en:"Sometimes beginners get Grawns and Grawfish confused. Any connoisseur will tell you that Grawfish are much bigger and have a much more sumptuous taste."};
descriptions["13191"]={cn:"皇家小龙虾的特征是又大又锋利的钳子。渔夫在捕获它们的时候，时常会被割断手指。",en:"You can recognize Royal Grawfish by their huge, razor-sharp pincers. It\'s not unusual for a fisherman to lose his fingers while trying to reel one in."};
descriptions["13192"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["13193"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["13194"]={cn:"谁想得到这么可爱的生物会掀起一场腥风血雨？",en:"Who\'d have guessed that this little cutie would grow up to lead revolutions?"};
descriptions["13195"]={cn:"咬一口，开始吹箫。",en:"Take a bite and prepare to get down with the trumpets of your palate."};
descriptions["13196"]={cn:"石头下面有一条鳗鱼，气味难闻...",en:"When there is an eel under a rock, it doesn\'t usually smell good... or so they say."};
descriptions["13197"]={cn:"据老渔夫说这条鳗鱼从天而降...原来这就是它炽热光环的来由！",en:"An old fishermen\'s tale says that this eel fell from the sky... So that explains its glowing aura!"};
descriptions["13198"]={cn:"对于我们来说，如果把你的手指放进虎鱼水槽，肯定很有意思。",en:"Put your fingers in the Piri Pirhiana tank: It\'ll be funny! Especially for us!"};
descriptions["13199"]={cn:"据说会传播致命细菌...",en:"It\'s said this fish propagates salmonella, ella, ella, ey, ey, ey..."};
descriptions["13200"]={cn:"除了好看好像也没什么别的用处了。用来在女士面前显摆吧，像公鸡那样昂首阔步。",en:"This Tench\'s crest isn\'t useful for anything, except for lookin\' good down at the fishcoteque."};
descriptions["13201"]={cn:"即便已经被做成盘中餐，这只鲨鱼仍然保持骑士风度。",en:"A shark which remains noble, even when doused in ketchup on your plate."};
descriptions["13216"]={cn:"能工巧匠的理想饰品！",en:"The ideal accessory for a super craftsman!"};
descriptions["13219"]={cn:"勾引幸运猫女士的最佳选择。",en:"A simple, effective dish to impress any Ecaflipette on a dinner date."};
descriptions["13222"]={cn:"松软的面包，夹着香脆的薯片，味道好极了。",en:"Squidgy, soft bread - fill with crisps for maximum effect."};
descriptions["13224"]={cn:"在南瓜世纪，即便是个南瓜平民也能吃到这种南瓜面包！",en:"For the umpteenth time, you don\'t need to be a country umpkin to eat this Pumpkin-flavored bread!"};
descriptions["13225"]={cn:"富含纤维素，调理消化系统。",en:"This high-fiber bread will keep your digestive system running like clockwork."};
descriptions["13226"]={cn:"在海滩上野餐的好选择。",en:"The bread of choice for picnics on the beach."};
descriptions["13227"]={cn:"什么？你还在指望豆沙馅以外的东西...？",en:"What? Were you expecting these little bread cakes to be stuffed with something other than Bean Juice...?"};
descriptions["13228"]={cn:"结实的面包，包你吃饱。",en:"A dense bread to really fill you up."};
descriptions["13229"]={cn:"如果你不喜欢吃面包，那么试试米饭吧。",en:"If you\'re not a bread guy or gal, stock up on these rice delights."};
descriptions["13230"]={cn:"让你的味蕾充满香甜可口的烘烤面包味。",en:"A pastry to bathe your taste buds in a bliss of sugar, ice, and all things nice."};
descriptions["13231"]={cn:"由美味的黄麻制成，富含益生菌。",en:"This bread is made out of all the yummy bacteria produced by the Sweat Jute plant."};
descriptions["13232"]={cn:"简单朴素的面包，无须任何广告也能大受欢迎。",en:"This simple bread doesn\'t need silly jokes to market itself; it\'s corny enough as it is."};
descriptions["13233"]={cn:"甜瓜的形状、甜瓜的风味，风味天然，富含自然营养。",en:"Melon-shaped and Melon-flavored, but with all the natural benefits of good ol\' bread."};
descriptions["13234"]={cn:"使用了葵花油的面包，照亮灰暗的日子！",en:"This Sunflower Oil bread will brighten up the darkest day!"};
descriptions["13235"]={cn:"谁能想到...这世界上居然有和西瓜一样爽脆香甜的面包。",en:"Who\'d have thunk it - a loaf of bread as sweet and refreshing as a Watermelon."};
descriptions["13236"]={cn:"手里拿着一根羽毛，仿佛可以飞起来！",en:"Now just hold a magic feather in your nose and you\'ll be able to fly!"};
descriptions["13238"]={cn:"你用一盏布满灰尘的油灯换到了这件衣服。绝对是笔好买卖！",en:"You got this costume in exchange for some old oil lamp that was way too dusty to use for anything. Definitely a good deal, champ!"};
descriptions["13239"]={cn:"在特别的日子里，穿上婚纱，举行舞会，为你的新奴...哦不，新郎戴上枷锁。",en:"Just the right outfit for that special day when you put the ball and chain on your new sla-\nuh, husband."};
descriptions["13240"]={cn:"价值三袋大麦粉。好吧，其实不是很多。但是想想你可以做多少麦粉小饼吧！",en:"A costume worth three sacks of barley flour. Alright, it\'s not very much, but just think of all the Tortikuri you could have made!"};
descriptions["13241"]={cn:"由花边和丝带装饰，穿上之后显得很漂亮。只是稍微走几步之后就会弄得浑身污秽。",en:"Decorated with lace and ribbon, with this costume you can be sure you\'ll stay looking good, despite being absolutely filthy from all that running around."};
descriptions["13242"]={cn:"看起来好像邪恶版本的阿里巴巴！",en:"Look like Baba\'s ally in this devious tunic!"};
descriptions["13243"]={cn:"能让你的敌人四处奔逃...你又要讲冷笑话了。",en:"A costume to have your enemies running for cover - the bells will warn them that you\'re coming to tell another one of your jokes."};
descriptions["13244"]={cn:"肯定会弄脏的，所以完全不用洗或者担心沾到污渍。就像高档的奶酪，只会随着时间流逝变得越来越好，当然也包括气味。",en:"Finally a naturally dirty costume that you\'re not afraid of getting grubby. You don\'t even have to wash it. Like good cheese, it gets better with time, smell included."};
descriptions["13245"]={cn:"你听到喵叫...",en:"If you stroke this costume often enough you might just hear it purr"};
descriptions["13246"]={cn:"哦啦啦！哦啦啦！哦雷雷雷...哦哦！",en:"Ole! Ola! Ole! Oleeeeee... Ow!"};
descriptions["13247"]={cn:"光鲜的衣着，人模狗样。",en:"A splendid set, so you can look handsome for your Pink Piwi and not too much like a Pingwin."};
descriptions["13248"]={cn:"你可以一整天穿着这件衣服，在田野里游走。",en:"You\'ll have a field day playing around in this costume."};
descriptions["13249"]={cn:"源自樱花之乡的设计，能为穿戴者带来天长地久的幸福生活。",en:"This cherry-tree design costume is supposed to bestow a long and happy life on whoever wears it."};
descriptions["13250"]={cn:"穿上它，出发去新世界！",en:"A costume headed straight for the new world!"};
descriptions["13251"]={cn:"煽动敌人的怒意，挑动追求者的欲望！",en:"An outfit capable of stirring up your enemies\' anger and your suitors\' ardent desire!"};
descriptions["13252"]={cn:"献给所有法式美食的爱好者！",en:"For all fans of Moogrr Rouge and Ribbitikibble!"};
descriptions["13253"]={cn:"十分可爱，散发着香甜可口的草莓味！",en:"An outfit which is super cute and smells of yummy-scrummy strawberries!"};
descriptions["13254"]={cn:"展现你的权威，受万人景仰！",en:"Show off your authority and become the toast of the taverns!"};
descriptions["13256"]={cn:"对于轻浮笨拙的冒险者来说是完美选择。",en:"This royal amulet is perfect for all those flighty, feather-brained adventures."};
descriptions["13330"]={cn:"至少在你尝试使用你的新技能的时候它不会进行反击，更重要的是，它不需要食物而且也不需要更换底座。",en:"At least this one won\'t answer back when you try out your new spells. What\'s more, he doesn\'t eat and you don\'t have to change his litter tray."};
descriptions["13331"]={cn:"真正的灌木，看起来像...假的。",en:"A real shrub that looks... Fake."};
descriptions["13332"]={cn:"漂亮的喷泉，用于装点庇护袋中的花园。",en:"A decorative fountain to spritz up your Haven Bag or Haven World."};
descriptions["13343"]={cn:"给好孩子糖果是一种传统...奶奶说这让他们茁壮成长。",en:"It\'s traditional to give children candy if they\'ve been good... Grandma says it makes them big and strong."};
descriptions["13344"]={cn:"给好孩子糖果是一种传统...奶奶说这让他们茁壮成长。",en:"It\'s traditional to give children candy if they\'ve been good... Grandma says it makes them big and strong."};
descriptions["13345"]={cn:"倒数三秒。三，二，一，走你！",en:"I have three seconds to tell you that this Canoon Powder is the boooooomb!"};
descriptions["13346"]={cn:"多买些给你的宠物吧。",en:"All pets love it!\nGeneric food for all pets and petsmounts."};
descriptions["13347"]={cn:"和你的朋友们整夜狂欢吧！",en:"This will keep your friends on their toes all night long!"};
descriptions["13358"]={cn:"使你的宠物恢复1点生命。",en:"This powder will restore a pet\'s HP by 1."};
descriptions["13359"]={cn:"篮子里有些什么？起司！",en:"What have you got in this basket, then? Cheese, cheese-uh-huh!"};
descriptions["13360"]={cn:"完全由树叶制成。当心不要让它被风吹走了！",en:"This little pouch is made entirely of leaves. Careful it doesn\'t fly away!"};
descriptions["13361"]={cn:"出自一位非常聪明的糖果师的配方，会将他本人的一部分知识传递给你。",en:"This candy was inspired by a very wise confectioner\'s recipe book and will transfer part of his knowledge to you."};
descriptions["13362"]={cn:"由一层尘土外衣包裹，将提高使用者的悟性。",en:"Well-preserved by a sturdy layer of dust, this candy will give great wisdom to whoever can stomach it."};
descriptions["13363"]={cn:"给好孩子糖果是一种传统...奶奶说这让他们茁壮成长。",en:"It\'s traditional to give children candy if they\'ve been good... Grandma says it makes them big and strong."};
descriptions["13364"]={cn:"给好孩子糖果是一种传统...奶奶说这让他们茁壮成长。",en:"It\'s traditional to give children candy if they\'ve been good... Grandma says it makes them big and strong."};
descriptions["13376"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["13378"]={cn:"一起来摇旗助威吧！",en:"Politics are in, baby!"};
descriptions["13408"]={cn:"回收掉。",en:"An old guild costume that\'s good for recycling now."};
descriptions["13409"]={cn:"展示公会的力量！",en:"Show off your guild colors for all to see!"};
descriptions["13410"]={cn:"献给创生之力的信徒。",en:"For those who believe in the power of Wakfu."};
