descriptions["13544"]={cn:"昂贵的披风，但是你穿起来帅气得像男模。",en:"This cape cost a fortune, but you feel like a male model in it, so what the neck!"};
descriptions["13545"]={cn:"成名的第一步是要穿上一双牢固的靴子，这样可以狠狠地踢别人的屁股。",en:"The first step to fame is some trusty boots to kick butt with."};
descriptions["13546"]={cn:"它吐了吐舌头，仿佛在嘲弄你。",en:"It almost looks as though this belt is sticking its tongue out to taunt you."};
descriptions["13547"]={cn:"小心！它不只会吞噬灵魂！",en:"Watch out! This ring might suck up more than just your soul!"};
descriptions["13548"]={cn:"装扮成吸血公爵的最佳选择！",en:"If you weren\'t pale and sickly already then this headgear is just right for you!"};
descriptions["13550"]={cn:"千万里你追寻着一个称号，就是这个啦，显摆一下蒸汽斗士有多厉害吧！",en:"All your life you\'ve been searching for something, and maybe this was it. Show the World what a Foggfighter you are!"};
descriptions["13551"]={cn:"械勒居然拨动了圣钟！这家伙疯了吗？",en:"Xelor has reset the divine clock. Who does that dude think he is?!"};
descriptions["13561"]={cn:"像狼皮一样引人注目...",en:"As seductive as a slab of Boowolf skin..."};
descriptions["13562"]={cn:"穿上这件性感的胸甲，你会让旁观者着迷的！",en:"You\'ll drive onlookers absolutely wild with this sexy breastplate!"};
descriptions["13563"]={cn:"让你挺拔坚硬如牛角！",en:"This helmet will make you as tough as old leather."};
descriptions["13564"]={cn:"穿上这双靴子后你身轻如猫，可以轻易撕碎敌人的皮肤。",en:"You\'ll be just as gracious as a feline in these boots but that doesn\'t mean that you can\'t tan someone\'s hide all the same."};
descriptions["13565"]={cn:"这个项链很紧，十分的紧，请在戴上它之前深吸一口气！",en:"As its name would indicate, this necklace chokes. Make sure you take a deep breath before you put it on!"};
descriptions["13566"]={cn:"保护需要保护的部位！",en:"This protects what needs to be protected!"};
descriptions["13567"]={cn:"让你在道场里发挥更多的威力！",en:"Allowing you to hit that little bit harder in the arena!"};
descriptions["13568"]={cn:"穿起来，拥有和兽人一样的脚臭！",en:"These boots\'ll make your feet smell like Bwork sweat!"};
descriptions["13569"]={cn:"喜欢近身战斗？好吧，带上这顶假发吧。它一点儿也不难闻，肯定是你自己的气味...",en:"Are you a fan of Gladiatrool combat? Well, wear this wig, made of Gladiatrool fibers, with pride. What? No, it doesn\'t smell at all - must just be you..."};
descriptions["13574"]={cn:"举起手来...这只戒指有点蹊跷！",en:"Hold up... There\'s something funny about this ring!"};
descriptions["13576"]={cn:"帽子的内衬有一股兔兔的骚味。",en:"The inside of this hat smells suspiciously like Wodents."};
descriptions["13577"]={cn:"四处游荡，取悦大人小孩。",en:"Clown around and brighten up the day for kids and grown-ups alike with this shiny, red, honking nose."};
descriptions["13580"]={cn:"比你粗壮的身材再大上一圈，记得时刻用手提着，这也是它的价值所在...",en:"Even if this belt is slightly too large for your muscular torso, we recommend you hold on to it. Its value will become clear..."};
descriptions["13581"]={cn:"属于一位著名的宝藏猎人。它怎么会在这儿...？",en:"This ring used to belong to a long-lost, illustrious Enutrof. How on earth did it end up here...?"};
descriptions["13582"]={cn:"闯过黑暗弗拉德的迷宫之后，你大可以自豪地带上这柄木剑，世人将会为你的顽强和勇气所倾倒。",en:"Carry this sword with pride as onlookers admire the tenacity and courage you bear having made it out alive from Dark Vlad\'s Maze."};
descriptions["13597"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["13607"]={cn:"能帮你轻松地打理生活。",en:"This accessory should help you contemplait life without dis-tress."};
descriptions["13608"]={cn:"和你习惯穿的传统风格裙子有些不同，这块兽皮让你回归石器时代！",en:"Not quite the standard you\'re used to, this hide takes you back to the stone age!"};
descriptions["13611"]={cn:"可爱的公仔，散发着一股巨魔的气味。",en:"This realistic cuddly toy comes with a free Trool-scented air freshener!"};
descriptions["13612"]={cn:"不要把它放进澡盆里...防水性很差...",en:"Don\'t try and put it in the bath - it doesn\'t take to water very well..."};
descriptions["13613"]={cn:"喔！好可爱的邪恶小夸夸！",en:"Oh! Such a cutey-wutesy, evil little Quaquack!"};
descriptions["13614"]={cn:"可以在泡澡的时候玩，如果靠近一点，你会发现它还有其他用途！",en:"This Quaquack can be used at bath time, and if you have the time to look a bit closer you might find that it has other purposes too!"};
descriptions["13615"]={cn:"抱着爱心兔安睡吧。",en:"You\'re sure to doze off with the Love Coney snuggled up against your chest."};
descriptions["13616"]={cn:"即便所有人都对你冷眼相对，靠枕依然能给你安全。",en:"This cushion hearts you, even if nobody else does!"};
descriptions["13617"]={cn:"晚上趁你不注意的时候，会扑向你。",en:"This cuddly toy will roll towards you in the night when you\'re not looking."};
descriptions["13618"]={cn:"趁你睡，要你命。",en:"This cuddly toy will haunt you whilst you sleep."};
descriptions["13619"]={cn:"整天追着你跑的公仔，只是想获得一个温暖的拥抱。",en:"This fluffy toy won\'t stop running after you until it gets what it wants: a warm, hearty cuddle."};
descriptions["13620"]={cn:"天使球比特，在你的庇护袋里做他爱做的事！",en:"Cupiddlypants, doing what he does best, right here in your Haven Bag!"};
descriptions["13621"]={cn:"香脆可口。",en:"A tasty treat that will make you shake your tail feather with joy!"};
descriptions["13622"]={cn:"稍稍呷一口，你会发现你上厕所的次数远远超过想象。",en:"One gulp of this stuff and you\'ll be passing through the Pit Stop faster than you can say Super Pup."};
descriptions["13623"]={cn:"富含钙质的冰冻饮料，绅士们值得一试！饮用前请摇匀。",en:"A frozen drink rich in calcium for all those respectable men who need to chill out!\nSheikh well before drinking."};
descriptions["13624"]={cn:"和宝藏猎人脸上的软毛一样柔软。快吃，很快就会化掉！",en:"As soft as an Enutrofette\'s facial hair, this sweet Cotton Candeh won\'t stick around for long!"};
descriptions["13625"]={cn:"咬一口...麻麻说小心牙齿坏掉！",en:"Take a bite into this candy Api... Just watch your teeth!"};
descriptions["13626"]={cn:"让你头发倒竖！",en:"The taste of this drink alone will make your hair stand on end!"};
descriptions["13627"]={cn:"快吃，要融化了！",en:"Quick, quick! It\'s dripping, it\'s dripping!"};
descriptions["13628"]={cn:"我们很晚也不睡，分享巨魔的故事，早晨醒来的时候，我正在做华夫饼干！",en:"We can stay up late, swapping Troolish stories, and in the morning, I\'m making Waffles!"};
descriptions["13629"]={cn:"鸡肉味，嘎嘣脆。嘉年华必备！",en:"Crunchy, cheeken-flavored cheeps, a Trool Fair favorite!"};
descriptions["13630"]={cn:"关键时刻的必备粮食。",en:"If things are getting critical, get your teeth around this Hazelnutella treat."};
descriptions["13634"]={cn:"空瓶子，随你装什么，只要它装得下。",en:"An empty vial that you can fill with whatever you want - assuming, of course, it fits in a vial."};
descriptions["13637"]={cn:"夸夸是很蠢的生物，智商远远低于豆芙和绵球，甚至比骑士还蠢。",en:"Tofus, Gobballs and even Iops can\'t hold a candle to the Quaquack when it comes to sheer idiocy."};
descriptions["13638"]={cn:"这是夸夸的食物里，唯一能保持他们的长嘴不弯曲的东西。",en:"These tidbits are the only thing that Quaquacks can eat without getting their beaks all bent up."};
descriptions["13639"]={cn:"宠物染料可以于宠物设定介面中更改。此物品已无用处，可以将其分解掉。",en:"Pet colorings can be changed in the pet settings interface. This item is obsolete; you can recycle it."};
