descriptions["13656"]={cn:"土鳖或不土鳖？这是一个问题。别纠结了，掷骰子决定吧。",en:"Do you or don\'t you? You do, but you don\'t... But then again, you do... I mean, it\'s cool if you don\'t... Do you?"};
descriptions["13657"]={cn:"你的邋遢正适合它！",en:"You are so skanky that you\'re worth it!"};
descriptions["13658"]={cn:"即便当你最好的朋友需要钱的时候，你也能做到一毛不拔。",en:"This breastplate will make sure you hold on to your last kama, even when your closest friend is in need."};
descriptions["13659"]={cn:"让你的每一步都带起一片飞扬的尘土，最大限度提升发现宝藏的能力。",en:"These boots will allow you to rake up the earth at high speeds for maximum treasure-finding ability."};
descriptions["13660"]={cn:"保护你的存粮躲过其他流浪汉的贪婪目光。",en:"This cloak will allow you to instantly hide your provisions from wandering eyes."};
descriptions["13661"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["13666"]={cn:"即使是在潮湿的状态下，这个袋子依然能够保持干爽，全靠它的防潮层才能保持干爽一整天！",en:"Even wet, this bag stays dry.\nWith an odor-fighting layer, stay dry all day!"};
descriptions["13667"]={cn:"当你无所适从的时候，这个可爱的玩具会用它柔软的羽毛和无边的智慧指引你。",en:"When you just don\'t know where to turn, this cuddly toy\'s super-soft feathers and endless wisdom will comfort you no end."};
descriptions["13668"]={cn:"阿玛克纳官方正式版。",en:"The official stuffed toy of Amakna."};
descriptions["13669"]={cn:"邦塔官方正式版。",en:"The official stuffed toy of Bonta."};
descriptions["13670"]={cn:"布拉克玛官方正式版。",en:"The official stuffed toy of Brakmar."};
descriptions["13671"]={cn:"萨弗基亚官方正式版。",en:"The official stuffed toy of Sufokia."};
descriptions["13672"]={cn:"看上去像真的一样，只是废话少了。",en:"It looks almost real. At least it doesn\'t talk as much."};
descriptions["13673"]={cn:"请用力哭，使劲哭。",en:"You can cry as much as you like into this cuddly-wuddly Ogrest."};
descriptions["13674"]={cn:"考虑到你不能把大角斗士带回家，你只好选择住下来了。",en:"Given that you can\'t take Gladiatrool home, you decided to settle for the miniature."};
descriptions["13675"]={cn:"拥抱黑暗！",en:"Come on over to the dark side!"};
descriptions["13676"]={cn:"现在你可以拥有属于你自己的如意门了！",en:"So you can imagine you have your very own trapdoor to somewhere exciting!"};
descriptions["13677"]={cn:"最可爱的黑鸦骑士！",en:"The Black Crow has never been cuter!"};
descriptions["13678"]={cn:"气味和真正的神圣绵球一样刺鼻。所以请保持你的庇护袋定期通风。",en:"This cuddly toy smells just as bad as the real Gobbsage, \nso make sure you air your Haven Bag properly on a regular basis!"};
descriptions["13679"]={cn:"内部充满了过期的巧克力馅。",en:"This cuddly toy is stuffed with out-of-date chocolate drops."};
descriptions["13680"]={cn:"在你的指尖滑行。\n每两周浇一次水。",en:"This cuddly toy will slide between your fingers. Water twice a week."};
descriptions["13681"]={cn:"尽管它的视线充满了恶意，你仍然忍不住想拥抱它。",en:"Despite its evil stare, you can\'t help but be seduced by this cutesy-wutesy, fluffy thing!"};
descriptions["13682"]={cn:"斯雷克绒毛玩具，看上去不太恶心...",en:"She doesn\'t seem quite so gross in fluffy form..."};
descriptions["13683"]={cn:"改进了缺点，几乎和原版一模一样！",en:"Almost as real as the original, without the disadvantages!"};
descriptions["13684"]={cn:"下次记得带纸...别怪我没提醒。",en:"If you twinkle when you spinkle... Be a sweetie and wipe the seatie."};
descriptions["13685"]={cn:"有多种颜色可供选择，但是这不重要。因为气球迟早要飞走。",en:"You can choose any color you want, but it won\'t really matter if you let it go into the air."};
