descriptions["13689"]={cn:"宝藏猎人保证你能被好运撞到腰！",en:"Enutrof has made sure you get a strike of luck!"};
descriptions["13691"]={cn:"这一称号授予在国家事务上表现活跃的人物。",en:"This title is given to those who have stood out as great political figures."};
