descriptions["13710"]={cn:"宠物染料可以于宠物设定介面中更改。此物品已无用处，可以将其分解掉。",en:"Pet colorings can be changed in the pet settings interface. This item is obsolete; you can recycle it."};
descriptions["13714"]={cn:"抖动尾巴上的羽毛！",en:"Shake your tail feathers!"};
descriptions["13715"]={cn:"即便是邪恶的夸夸也可以抖羽毛！",en:"Even an Evil Quaquack can shake its tail feathers!"};
descriptions["13716"]={cn:"你看上去和你的偶像一样，不过你最好永远见不到他！",en:"You\'ll be able to look like your idol, but here\'s hoping you never meet him in person!"};
descriptions["13717"]={cn:"小心点，别拿弓乱射...",en:"Careful with that bow, Eugene..."};
descriptions["13718"]={cn:"你喜欢浑身颤抖的感觉吗？",en:"You love the shivers this costume sends running all over your body!"};
descriptions["13719"]={cn:"宝藏猎人把他知道的一切储存到了这块糖果里。",en:"Enutrof has instilled everything he knows into this yummy little treat."};
descriptions["13720"]={cn:"你看起来很像穿着国庆节装束的三姆大叔！",en:"You too can look like my Uncle Sammy in his very best patriotic celebratory attire!"};
descriptions["13721"]={cn:"穿上你国庆节的装束吧。人们会彻底无视你。",en:"Show off in your very best patriotic celebratory attire. People will have nothing on you!"};
descriptions["13722"]={cn:"根据阿玛克纳考古学家最新研究，这件披风也许属于某个秘密结社。",en:"It has been suggested that this cape, which was recently unveiled by Amaknian Arkaeologists, might be a sign of affiliation to a slightly secret society."};
descriptions["13724"]={cn:"像你去年夏天那样尽情扭动吧。",en:"Twist like you did last summer, or like you did last year if you prefer."};
descriptions["13725"]={cn:"如果你跳得够好，我们就让你成为这片海的管理者。",en:"If you dance this well enough we might let you become a crimebuster of the sea."};
descriptions["13726"]={cn:"好好练，也许你会成为新的时尚领路人。",en:"Practice this dance enough and it might become the vogue."};
descriptions["13727"]={cn:"让节奏引导你的身体。",en:"Let yourself get carried away by the rhythm."};
descriptions["13728"]={cn:"给脚底抹点油，然后用力摇摆！",en:"Grease up your feet to really shimmy and shake!"};
descriptions["13738"]={cn:"今日星座运势...你可以解决困扰长期困扰你的所有问题！",en:"Your horoscope says... you\'re able to face all the problems that bother you normally from day to day."};
descriptions["13742"]={cn:"今日星运预测...不要让别人踩到你的脚趾头！",en:"Your horoscope says... don\'t let other people trample on your toes!"};
descriptions["13746"]={cn:"今日星座运势：没有什么可以吓到你的，放轻松！",en:"Your horoscope says... nothing will frighten you today, which is a weight off your shoulders!"};
descriptions["13750"]={cn:"今日星座运势：没有人可以影响你今天的心情，你有能力克服一切困难。",en:"Your horoscope says... other people\'s problems won\'t affect you today and you\'ll be able to rise against any conflicts encountered."};
descriptions["13754"]={cn:"拿这玩意儿砸敌人的脸就对了！",en:"There\'s nothing left to do but throw this at the heads of your enemies!"};
descriptions["13758"]={cn:"今日星座运势...抬起你的头来！",en:"Your horoscope says... hold your head high!"};
descriptions["13762"]={cn:"保护真正的骑士！",en:"Protects the chivalrous."};
descriptions["13767"]={cn:"保持你的双脚干燥，免受伤害。但是热得要命！",en:"The perfect footwear for all your cavernous adventures."};
descriptions["13770"]={cn:"当你身处异常狭窄的通道里的时候，这对护肩能完好地保护你。",en:"These super-sharp epaulettes double up as weapons for when you\'re in dire straits!"};
descriptions["13777"]={cn:"即便是和平年代，你也会想要挥舞几下长枪。",en:"Even in times of peace you want a slice of the action."};
descriptions["13781"]={cn:"作为一名杀手永远知道何时是揭示自己身份的正确时间。",en:"An assassin knows how to conceal his identity when push comes to shove."};
descriptions["13782"]={cn:"向旁观者彰显你是个英勇的骑士，即便隐藏在盔甲底下的只是个抠脚汉。",en:"This helmet will give onlookers the impression that you\'re a valiant knight, even if underneath it you\'re just a big fat coward!"};
descriptions["13786"]={cn:"轻盈的胸甲，即便是最凶险的场合也能应对。",en:"This breastplate is so light that it adapts to all situations, even the most risky!"};
descriptions["13790"]={cn:"职业杀手总是警惕着背后的敌人！",en:"An assassin protects his behind at all times!"};
descriptions["13794"]={cn:"你说什么？杀手不穿裹腿？那么他们把武器藏在哪里呢？",en:"What do you mean, assassins don\'t wear leggings? Where else would they hide their most powerful weapons?"};
descriptions["13798"]={cn:"既沉重又不实用的宝剑，想在布恩特卡酒馆的传奇蓝调之夜交几个朋友的话，它是你必备的。",en:"This heavy, impractical sword is a must-have for anyone who wants to make friends at the Burnteca Tavern\'s legendary RnB nights."};
descriptions["13802"]={cn:"这件短衣属于一个古代文明的遗产，他们依靠精神力量和新鲜的水生活！",en:"This tunic forms part of the patrimony of an ancient civilization that used to live off of high spirits and fresh water alone!"};
descriptions["13806"]={cn:"据说曾经属于一个勇猛的绵球。有一天他突然无声无息地消失了。在那以后，总是有人说在该地区看到一个长着翅膀的绵球出现。",en:"A story says that this helmet used to grace the head of a courageous Gobball. He disappeared without a trace one day and ever since, people have reported sightings of a winged face in the area where he used to live."};
descriptions["13810"]={cn:"很久以前有这样一个习俗：年轻的勇士拿着肩甲往头盔上狠狠地砸几下，希望大脑心智早日成熟。",en:"An old custom was for young warriors on the verge of adulthood to smack their epaulettes off their helmets in order to knock the mind into shape."};
descriptions["13814"]={cn:"原始人经常外出，靠打猎谋生。因此他们需要优质的靴子...",en:"This ancient civilization used to walk a lot and lived essentially on hunting. They therefore needed very good shoes..."};
descriptions["13818"]={cn:"属于某个古老民族，象征着他们曾经的财富和辉煌。",en:"The cape of this ancient civilization is a reflection of all the wealth that it possessed in the past."};
descriptions["13825"]={cn:"据说这顶头盔获得了神之祝福，可以让拥有者听到10卡里以外的卡玛声！",en:"They say this helmet got the gods\' seal of approval for the peculiar sound it makes, which grants the wearer impeccable hearing capable of detecting coins from 10 kilokameters away!"};
descriptions["13826"]={cn:"为你带来好运，在拥挤的人群中能帮你找到前进方向。",en:"This ornamental piece will bring you good luck and help you find your way through crowds a-thronging."};
descriptions["13830"]={cn:"你和你的祖先脚踏着同一片土地。",en:"Wear these boots and you\'ll unearth a lot of dirt on your ancestors."};
descriptions["13834"]={cn:"大地母亲在忽悠着你。",en:"This cloak will give you a mysterious side designed by Mother Nature herself."};
descriptions["13838"]={cn:"为喜欢我们的既无脑又长毛的朋友的玩家专门设计！",en:"This helmet was made for all those fans of our brainless feathered friends!"};
descriptions["13842"]={cn:"这顶头盔可以听见声音。\n远古的回响？又或者只是你想多了...？",en:"This helmet hears voices. \nAncient voices? Or is this all just a figment of your imagination...?"};
descriptions["13849"]={cn:"这件斗篷会惊动你的很多敌人。\n你是否命中注定要战胜最强者？",en:"This cloak will disturb your many enemies. \nIs it decidedly your destiny to bring down the strongest?"};
descriptions["13855"]={cn:"小小的糕点，缓解饥饿。",en:"This little cake will relieve your pain."};
descriptions["13858"]={cn:"揉得粉碎，好比你的尊严。",en:"It\'s falling to pieces, much like your dignity."};
descriptions["13862"]={cn:"往那个正在哆嗦的人身上扔过去。",en:"Try throwing this at someone when it\'s doughing."};
descriptions["13865"]={cn:"当你咬不动其他面包的时候，尝尝这块面包吧。",en:"Try this filling bread when the other loaves just won\'t cut it."};
descriptions["13870"]={cn:"新鲜的酥皮，只融于口不融于手，松脆可口。",en:"This freshly whipped meringue is stiff enough to stand on its own and wet enough to shine."};
descriptions["13877"]={cn:"讨厌头部被滑溜的蜗牛壳打到？\n多吃点美味的汤团，试图改变你的命运。",en:"Fed up of taking knocks to the head?\nChange your destiny by eating these delicious dumplings."};
descriptions["13882"]={cn:"一种碳酸饮料...喝了容易激动。",en:"To make give your punch a bit more... punch."};
descriptions["13886"]={cn:"很美味的一种馅饼，用罐装牛肉做的...你也可以用敌人的肉来做！",en:"This is the good type - the one with corned beef. You can make it out of your enemies!"};
descriptions["13888"]={cn:"如果感到高兴我们就来击掌吧。",en:"Don\'t be thinking this is a story all about how your life got twisted, turned upside-down... it\'s just a secret handshake."};
descriptions["13889"]={cn:"如果感到很高兴我们就来击击掌吧。",en:"Don\'t be thinking this is a story all about how your life got twisted, turned upside-down... it\'s just a secret handshake."};
descriptions["13891"]={cn:"亲吻，是用一张嘴堵住另一张，把所有的甜言蜜语都封死在心里。",en:"Kiss me, down by the House of Respite... Lead me, into the Three Pistes\' Cave... Bring bring, bring your Makabraxe... We\'ll take the trail marked on Yew-Teeny\'s map... Oh!"};
descriptions["13893"]={cn:"还有别的么？",en:"What else?"};
descriptions["13896"]={cn:"更待何时？",en:"What else?"};
descriptions["13904"]={cn:"比任何喷射性呕吐物的速度都要快！",en:"This fairy will launch into the air faster than projectile vomit!"};
descriptions["13905"]={cn:"吓跑你的敌人。",en:"This Fairywork might flare up your adversaries."};
descriptions["13906"]={cn:"当心你的脚下！",en:"Mind your feet!"};
descriptions["13907"]={cn:"爆炸后呈现出七色彩虹！",en:"Bursting with rainbow colors!"};
descriptions["13908"]={cn:"爆炸后呈现十四色彩虹！",en:"Bursting with rainbow colors within rainbow colors!"};
descriptions["13909"]={cn:"烟火在制造过程中，不小心掉进了熊猫武僧的酒桶里。",en:"This little fairy fell into a Pandawa\'s barrel of milk when it was little."};
descriptions["13945"]={cn:"没有比一边看球赛，一边喝爽口的绵球球啤酒更好的享受了！",en:"There\'s nothing better than a delicious, refreshing root beer to kick off a match!"};
descriptions["13948"]={cn:"具有神奇的额外功效，其他胸甲做梦也想不到。",en:"This breastplate will have a certain extra something that no other will."};
descriptions["13949"]={cn:"勉强可以一穿的靴子。",en:"These boots are just about wearable."};
descriptions["13950"]={cn:"保护你不被菜鸟弓手的乱箭射中面门。",en:"This helmet will protect your face from oncoming arrows launched by inexperienced Cras."};
descriptions["13951"]={cn:"外形一般，但是我们保证你穿起来很酷！",en:"It might not look like anything special but you\'ll look cool wearing this cloak, promise."};
descriptions["13952"]={cn:"保护你们的心脏。",en:"Protects the chivalrous."};
descriptions["13953"]={cn:"你在地上捡到了这件胸甲。你真走运！",en:"This breastplate was found kicking around on the ground. Lucky you!"};
descriptions["13954"]={cn:"完美的头带，把头发束起来。避免像个疯了的植物术士一样把头发甩来甩去。",en:"This headband will hold your hair in place perfectly, stopping you from flicking it around like a hot Sadidette that needs cooling down."};
descriptions["13955"]={cn:"独特的自然透气系统，穿起来十分舒坦。下雨的时候别穿。",en:"These boots aren\'t very practical when it\'s raining, but they\'re incredibly pleasant to wear thanks to their integrated natural airing system."};
descriptions["13956"]={cn:"即便是流浪汉，也可以变犀利哥！",en:"Even vagabonds can look good!"};
descriptions["13958"]={cn:"...你丢东西了...很重要的东西... *闻闻* 你的肥皂...你弄丢了肥皂...",en:"...You\'ve lost something... something very important... *sniff sniff* Your soap... you\'ve lost your soap..."};
descriptions["13959"]={cn:"明白了...明白了...恩...",en:"I see... I see... Hmmmm..."};
descriptions["13960"]={cn:"...我看到了灰尘...灰尘还有...灰常沉。",en:"...I see dirt... ...dirt and difficulty..."};
descriptions["13961"]={cn:"...身处险境的冒险者...",en:"...an adventurer at peril..."};
descriptions["13962"]={cn:"取破气球一只以及后院的少许铁屑，做个面具。然后取一个外国名字...每次都很有意思。",en:"Take a broken balloon and some scrap metal from behind your house to make a mask, and give it an exotic name - works every time."};
descriptions["13963"]={cn:"当你身处异常狭窄的通道里的时候，这对护肩能完好地保护你。",en:"These epaulettes will protect your shoulders when you\'re in a particularly sharp narrow passage."};
descriptions["13964"]={cn:"洞穴冒险的完美选择。",en:"The perfect footwear for all your cavernous adventures."};
descriptions["13965"]={cn:"有规律地微微跳动着，在你探索洞穴的时候鼓舞激励着你。",en:"This helmet pulses at a regular pace, inciting and exciting you all at the same time during your cavernous adventures."};
descriptions["13966"]={cn:"这是你临终前看到的最后一样东西。",en:"This breastplate is the last thing you\'ll see before your eternal rest."};
descriptions["13967"]={cn:"这是你临终前看到的最后一样东西。",en:"This helmet is the last thing you\'ll see before eternal rest."};
descriptions["13968"]={cn:"这是你临终前看到的最后一样东西。",en:"This helmet is the last thing you\'ll see before eternal rest."};
descriptions["13969"]={cn:"十分闷热的胸甲，穿久之后散发着一股哞哞臭味。",en:"You\'ll be smoking hot in this breastplate but will smell of smoked Moogrr if you keep it on for too long."};
descriptions["13970"]={cn:"这双炽热的靴子能让你步步生辉。",en:"These white-hot boots will set your steps on fire."};
descriptions["13971"]={cn:"如果觉得热，可以摘下来透透气。",en:"If you get a bit hot, air your head."};
descriptions["13972"]={cn:"肩甲上释放出的热量，能迅速缓解背部风湿痛。",en:"The heat generated by these epaulettes will instantly relieve your back pain."};
descriptions["13973"]={cn:"醒醒吧，你不会变成圣斗士的。",en:"Your chances of seeing a gold saint are as slim as a Schnek\'s of seeing the stars."};
descriptions["13974"]={cn:"醒醒吧，你不会变成圣斗士的。",en:"Your chances of seeing a gold saint are as slim as a Schnek\'s of seeing the stars."};
descriptions["13975"]={cn:"醒醒吧，你不会变成圣斗士的。",en:"Your chances of seeing a gold saint are as slim as a Schnek\'s of seeing the stars."};
descriptions["13976"]={cn:"只有当你升天之时，才能体会到这顶头盔的非凡之处。",en:"The significance of this helmet will become clear as you breathe your last breath."};
descriptions["13977"]={cn:"只有当你升天之时，才能体会到这对护肩的非凡之处。",en:"The significance of this helmet will become clear as you breathe your last breath."};
descriptions["13978"]={cn:"只有当你升天之时，才能体会到这件胸甲的非凡之处。",en:"The significance of this breastplate will become clear as you breathe your last breath."};
descriptions["13979"]={cn:"以一位著名女战士的名字命名。不幸的是，她已往生极乐。愿她永享安宁...你还在等什么？还不快出发！",en:"This helmet is named after a well-known warrior who was also the only daughter of eternal rest. May she rest in peace... Well, what are you waiting for? Get thudding!"};
descriptions["13980"]={cn:"以一位著名女战士的名字命名。不幸的是，她已往生极乐。愿她永享安宁...你还在等什么？还不快出发！",en:"These epaulettes are named after a well-known warrior who was also the only daughter of eternal rest. May she rest in peace... Well, what are you waiting for? Get thudding!"};
descriptions["13981"]={cn:"以一位著名女战士的名字命名。不幸的是，她已往生极乐。愿她永享安宁...你还在等什么？还不快出发！",en:"This helmet is named after a well-known warrior who was also the only daughter of eternal rest. May she rest in peace... Well, what are you waiting for? Get thudding!"};
descriptions["13982"]={cn:"保护你的双脚免受潮湿和伤害的侵袭，但是对于高热却无能为力！",en:"The perfect footwear for all your cavernous adventures."};
descriptions["13983"]={cn:"当你身处异常狭窄的通道里的时候，这对护肩能完好地保护你。",en:"These epaulettes will protect your shoulders when you\'re in a particularly sharp narrow passage."};
descriptions["13984"]={cn:"向旁观者彰显你是个英勇的骑士，即便隐藏在盔甲底下的只是个抠脚汉。",en:"This helmet will give onlookers the impression that you\'re a valiant knight, even if underneath it you\'re just a big fat coward!"};
descriptions["13985"]={cn:"保护好勇士。",en:"Protects the chivalrous."};
descriptions["13986"]={cn:"保护你免受暗箭袭击。",en:"The finish on this breastplate makes sure that you\'ll be protected from fast-approaching arrows."};
descriptions["13987"]={cn:"制甲师公会的最新产品。现在你成为了真正的猛男！",en:"The Guild of Armorers is proud to present their latest epaulette model. Now you can be a macho macho man!"};
descriptions["13988"]={cn:"如果这双靴子不隔热的话，也许就是制甲师公会的最佳作品了。",en:"If these boots didn\'t hold in the heat so much they\'d probably be one of the best creations from the Guild of Armorers."};
descriptions["13989"]={cn:"没有什么东西比这两个恰到好处的角更能展示你的男子“汗”气概了。",en:"Nothing says \'I\'m manly\' better than these two large, well-placed horns."};
descriptions["13990"]={cn:"虽然看起来像拖把，实际上却是制甲师公会最坚韧的作品之一。",en:"OK. Given, it looks a bit like a mop, but this cloak is one of the most resistant cloaks proposed by the Guild of Armorers."};
descriptions["13991"]={cn:"安静！在你结束战斗之后，你浑身上下散发着恶魔玫瑰的致命气味。",en:"Don\'t kick up a stink! These boots will leave you coming out of a fight smelling like anything but a Demonic Rose."};
descriptions["13992"]={cn:"不要吵闹！这顶帽子在你脱离战斗之后闻起来像恶魔玫瑰一样迷人。",en:"Don\'t kick up a stink! These boots will leave you coming out of a fight smelling like anything but a Demonic Rose."};
descriptions["13993"]={cn:"别臭美了！这件运动夹克让你在战斗结束之后，浑身上下散发着恶魔玫瑰的致命气味。",en:"Don\'t kick up a stink! These boots will leave you coming out of a fight smelling like anything but a Demonic Rose."};
descriptions["13994"]={cn:"别引起波动！这双靴子会帮你脱离任何状态的战斗，邪恶玫瑰除外。",en:"Don\'t kick up a stink! These boots will leave you coming out of a fight smelling like anything but a Demonic Rose."};
descriptions["13995"]={cn:"不仅让你的腋下潮湿，还散发出一股兽...哦等等，那是你身上的气味...",en:"These epaulettes will not only make your armpits sweat, but also give off a beautiful scent of BO... Oh wait, that\'s you..."};
descriptions["13996"]={cn:"汗流浃背！",en:"This helmet will make you sweat from head to toe!"};
descriptions["14033"]={cn:"宠物装备可以于宠物设定介面中更改。此物品已无用处，可以将其分解掉。",en:"Pet equipment can be changed in the pet settings interface. This item is obsolete; you can recycle it."};
descriptions["14037"]={cn:"来呀来呀，来砸我呀...哎呀...",en:"I threw a pie and I liked it, all that custard inside it... I threw a pie just to try it, I sure hope Ogrest don\'t mind it..."};
descriptions["14038"]={cn:"始终散发着诱人的果香。猴子们会拼命追着你跑！",en:"This cloak diffuses a fruity aroma all day long. The monkeys will be going ape just to get to you!"};
descriptions["14039"]={cn:"如果你还独守空房、垂泪伤心，你需要的是火辣法杖。",en:"If you\'re sitting there, eating your heart out, you need a Hot Staff."};
descriptions["14040"]={cn:"传说宝藏猎人是含着金汤匙出生的。噗噗！",en:"They say that Enutrofs are born with a golden spoon in their mouths. Amfufu!"};
descriptions["14041"]={cn:"这枚戒指被钉到了手指上。取下来估计会见血。",en:"Given that this ring was stapled onto your finger, expect a bit of blood when you decide to take it off."};
descriptions["14042"]={cn:"每天提供五块五克拉重的萝卜，营养均衡。",en:"This ring provides you with your five a day."};
descriptions["14043"]={cn:"穿几天之后，你会发现有虫子爬到脚上。",en:"These boots, made out of leftover soup ingredients, were a gift from Auntie Cranny. Waste not, want not is all very well, but for a couple of days now you\'ve been sure there are maggots crawling around between your toes..."};
descriptions["14044"]={cn:"这货不是靴子，这货不是靴子...",en:"Please tell me those are boots..."};
descriptions["14045"]={cn:"孩子们！该上床睡觉了！",en:"Boiiing! Time for bed!"};
descriptions["14046"]={cn:"像鳄鱼的鼻子一样坚硬多鳞。一旦扣上腰带扣，就很难松开。",en:"This belt\'s buckle is as hard and scaly as a crocodile\'s snout. Once you snap it closed, there\'s no way you\'re getting it open again."};
descriptions["14047"]={cn:"穿着出去吓唬超人。",en:"Team with glowsticks for a fail-safe going-out look."};
descriptions["14048"]={cn:"为踢绵球球的孩子们以及邋遢的食客们特地准备。当然你属于后者。",en:"For Gobbowl wonderkids and messy eaters. You only fit into the second category, unfortunately."};
descriptions["14049"]={cn:"吓得你在半夜里穿着睡衣逃出居住的小镇。",en:"This hat will make you want to run through the town in your nightwear."};
descriptions["14050"]={cn:"邋里邋遢的冒险者带着依然天真的眼神打量着周围，操着滑稽的口音讲冒险故事，你觉得他们毫不起眼。但是当他们戴上这顶帽子的时候，周围的女士的眼神突然由\"你想也别想\"变成\"我可以摸下你的帽子吗？\"没人知道为什么。奇迹每天都在发生。",en:"Wonders never cease!"};
descriptions["14055"]={cn:"一块可口的糖果，垂死挣扎之时尤其有用。",en:"A tasty treat that will come in handy when you need to survive."};
descriptions["14057"]={cn:"变身传奇的黑鸦骑士吧！",en:"Become the legendary Black Crow!"};
descriptions["14058"]={cn:"你看上去和你的偶像一样，不过你最好永远见不到他！",en:"You\'ll be able to look like your idol, but here\'s hoping you never meet him in person!"};
