descriptions["14115"]={cn:"闪耀着光芒的头盔，十分有用。在寒冷的冬天，保证你双耳温暖。",en:"An incandescent helmet that is very good at keeping your ears warm during those chilly winters."};
descriptions["14116"]={cn:"夏天的烈日仍然不够火辣，这件胸甲给你再添一把火。",en:"As if the summer sun wasn\'t enough, here\'s a breastplate which aspires to be a radiator."};
descriptions["14117"]={cn:"一脚踢飞所有拦路的绵球球。",en:"These Gobbalrog Boots will allow you to give a good boot to any flaming Gobbowl Ball coming your way."};
descriptions["14118"]={cn:"你看起来精神极了！皮肤过敏者慎用。同时也要当心屁股后面喷出火来。",en:"With this belt, you\'re sure to be full of beans! Not suitable for those with sensitive skin. Beware of backfire."};
descriptions["14119"]={cn:"传奇的宝剑，曾经属于一位伊欧普王子。他在绵矛革的肚子里挣扎过一段时间。现在，炎之哀伤又饿了...",en:"This legendary, icy sword was formerly carried by a Iop prince. His stay in the Gobbalrog\'s stomach made the sword glow and become even more powerful."};
descriptions["14120"]={cn:"不停喷射着火焰。曾经属于一个强大的法师，在一场和绵矛革的战斗中损坏了。",en:"This wand bears an almighty flame. It used to belong to a powerful mage and got terribly broken during an epic fight with a Gobbalrog."};
descriptions["14121"]={cn:"一手当关，万夫莫开！",en:"With this on your arm, you can be sure of one thing... They shall not pass!"};
descriptions["14122"]={cn:"使用别人的脚穿越炽热的岩浆实在是太惬意了，看看它们还有很多其他的方便...我是说便利，便利快捷。",en:"It\'s always easier to walk across lava with someone else\'s feet on. These have the added benefit of looking grood... I mean good. And great. Great and good."};
descriptions["14123"]={cn:"这些炙热的熔岩会给那些妄图佩戴这对肩甲的人一个难忘的教训。",en:"These hot coals will teach all those friends who use you as a shoulder to cry on a lesson."};
descriptions["14124"]={cn:"唯一能获取这件披风的方式是给绵矛革吹吹冷风，然后趁他哆嗦的时候偷走披风。",en:"The only known way to obtain this cloak is to give Magmog a cold and then whisk it off of his back at the most opportune moment."};
descriptions["14125"]={cn:"光晕是什么？从没玩过！",en:"As the famous enraged Iop once cried out: Halo? What?! he\'s never even played it!"};
descriptions["14126"]={cn:"近距离跟踪一只熔岩绵球，就能找到这些仍然带着火星的余烬。",en:"These glowing embers can often be found by closely following a Gobbalrog."};
descriptions["14127"]={cn:"纪念你英勇地与绵矛革作战，扑灭熊熊烈火。",en:"A battle trophy to remind you of that one time when you told Magmog: YOU\'RE FIRED!"};
descriptions["14128"]={cn:"这件蕴含强大力量的胸甲被一股无名的气息所包裹，卷卷的，有点娘。",en:"This breastplate\'s curly virility is counteracted by the ectoplasmic gloop all over it. Talk about ruining the mood."};
descriptions["14129"]={cn:"用于联结喀努斯的灵魂和神圣绵球的躯壳。属于灵体的强大法器...你能够驾驭这股强大的力量吗？",en:"This piece of jewelry was used to link Excarnus\'s soul to Gobbsage\'s ethereal body. A powerful artifact in the hands of an Excarnate... Do you really think you\'re capable of using its power?"};
descriptions["14130"]={cn:"作为气嘘者友好的主人曾经指出，这个靴子会给你带来各种各样的气势。",en:"As Gasper the friendly host once pointed out, these boots give you all sorts of airs and graces."};
descriptions["14131"]={cn:"这段薄纱能让覆盖着的恶灵隐身。很多人为了找到这件稀世珍宝而付出了本来就不怎么正常的理智。",en:"A transparent veil which enables excarnates to become invisible. Many a man is pushing up daisies after trying too hard to obtain this precious item."};
descriptions["14132"]={cn:"也许有点小，却承载着神圣绵球的灵魂之力，这股力量多年前被喀努斯吸取了。舔一口，有股干草的味道。",en:"It may be small, but this ring contains a fragment of Gobbsage\'s essence, absorbed long ago by Excarnus. Pop it in your mouth. It tastes like angry, digested hay."};
descriptions["14134"]={cn:"散发着一股充满野性的气味，让你忍不住想冲着满月嚎叫。",en:"This cloak has a beastly smell that risks causing undesirable secondary effects that will send you howling to the moon."};
descriptions["14135"]={cn:"用于在南瓜节化妆舞会上扮成狂狼...记得在亲吻心上人的时候拿下来！",en:"These fangs are just what you need to complete your Moowolf Al Howin\'s outfit... Just remember to take them off if you\'re kissing your sweetheart."};
descriptions["14136"]={cn:"穿上这个胸甲，上看下看左看右看，怎么看你都像...像头野兽。",en:"With one of these ferocious specimens on your front and one on your back, you\'ll look like... well, a beast with two backs."};
descriptions["14137"]={cn:"穿上它，可以让你涉足那些无法到达的地方。注意，在家里或者办公室的地板上就不要穿了。",en:"An accessory made for scratching hard-to-get-to places - just what you needed! A word of advice, though: with claws like that, you shouldn\'t use it anywhere... sensitive."};
descriptions["14138"]={cn:"转交这柄匕首的时候要小心了。它靠鲜血为生，无论是敌人的还是主人的。每个月必须喂食七天。",en:"Careful who you give this dagger to. It feeds on the blood of its victims, or on that of its owner, one week per month."};
descriptions["14140"]={cn:"一个集齐轻柔，舒适，飘逸，厚实于一身的羽毛护肩，不正是你对敌中需要的重要装备吗！",en:"A soft, comfortable, floaty, three-ply, feathery neck-dress. Just what you need to wipe enemies out!"};
descriptions["14141"]={cn:"赋予佩戴者的双重人格。引诱你的黑暗的一面。",en:"A powerful piece of jewelry that gives its bearer a second personality. Something to bring out your dark side!"};
descriptions["14142"]={cn:"由白鸦羽毛制成的稀有物品。获取它的唯一途径是击败黑鸦骑士...据说他死的时候羽毛会变成白色。",en:"A very rare item made of white crow feathers. The only way to get those is to kill a Black Crow... It\'s said that they turn white when they die."};
descriptions["14143"]={cn:"潮流选择，泡吧必备。即便是在漆黑之中，离着很远都看得到。",en:"A very trendy belt, ideal for clubbing. Thanks to its high visibility, this belt can be spotted from a distance, even when it\'s pitch black."};
descriptions["14144"]={cn:"戴着这对翅膀，直面危险挑战。虽然看起来像天使，但是穿起来难受极了！",en:"Fly into the face of danger with these wings. As angelic as they might seem, they\'re devilishly uncomfortable!"};
descriptions["14145"]={cn:"这尊华丽的雕像为你的庇护袋添增几分品味。有时候可能会听到一些咯咯声，但别在意。",en:"This magnificent statue would make a tasteful addition to your Haven Bag. You may hear some little giggling sounds from time to time, but pay them no mind."};
descriptions["14146"]={cn:"宠物染料可以于宠物设定介面中更改。此物品已无用处，可以将其分解掉。",en:"Pet colorings can be changed in the pet settings interface. This item is obsolete; you can recycle it."};
descriptions["14147"]={cn:"温顺可爱！",en:"So sweet and cute and Milimoowolfy!"};
descriptions["14148"]={cn:"宠物装备可以于宠物设定介面中更改。此物品已无用处，可以将其分解掉。",en:"Pet equipment can be changed in the pet settings interface. This item is obsolete; you can recycle it."};
