descriptions["14152"]={cn:"速度奇快，能轻易躲开你的攻击。",en:"This little Arachnee will very quickly dodge your huggles."};
descriptions["14156"]={cn:"宠物装备可以于宠物设定介面中更改。此物品已无用处，可以将其分解掉。",en:"Pet equipment can be changed in the pet settings interface. This item is obsolete; you can recycle it."};
descriptions["14157"]={cn:"比有血有肉的宠物更加忠诚，勾爪机器人永远跟随着你。",en:"More loyal than an organic pet, the Clawbot will follow you absolutely everywhere."};
descriptions["14162"]={cn:"历尽艰险的你赢得的奖励。你可以用这枚奖章兑换装备。",en:"You can trade in this hard-won token for pieces of equipment."};
descriptions["14163"]={cn:"历尽艰险的你赢得的奖励。你可以用这枚奖章兑换装备。",en:"You can trade in this hard-won token for pieces of equipment."};
descriptions["14164"]={cn:"历尽艰险的你赢得的奖励。你可以用这枚奖章兑换装备。",en:"You can trade in this hard-won token for pieces of equipment."};
descriptions["14165"]={cn:"烫得难以拿捏！快点在它烧穿你的口袋，烫伤你的皮肤之前用掉！",en:"It\'s almost too hot to handle! Quick, spend it before it burns a hole in your pocket and then your epidermis!"};
descriptions["14167"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["14168"]={cn:"将奖章投入阿尔玛纳兑奖机，你将获得丰厚奖励。\n阿尔玛纳兑奖机在阿斯图布森林的天书圣坛里。",en:"If you pop this this well-deserved token into an Almanax Machine you\'ll be lucratively rewarded.\nThe machine can be found in the Temple of Scriptures in Astrub Forest."};
descriptions["14186"]={cn:"此升华能装进遗物物品，提升穿戴者的能力。",en:"This sublimation fits into a relic item to increase the wearer\'s stats."};
descriptions["14191"]={cn:"当你穿好这套高科技服装后，你就能追随你最喜欢的艺术潮流，说不定你也能创造一股潮流。",en:"When this high-tech costume is equipped, you can follow the flux of your favorite artists and, who knows, maybe even give off your own."};
descriptions["14207"]={cn:"漂亮的霓家套件，存放漂亮的小东西。",en:"A gorgeous Ikiakit for those who collect beautiful things."};
descriptions["14215"]={cn:"社交不顺吗？来只烤龙鸟。",en:"Social life looking murky? Eat a stuffed Dragoturkey."};
descriptions["14254"]={cn:"把你变成一只可爱的小喵喵。",en:"This pretty little treat will turn you into a pretty little Bow Meow."};
descriptions["14255"]={cn:"能将你变成刚刚死去的幽灵。",en:"This strange liquor will transform you into a fresh-from-the-dead Ghostof."};
