descriptions["14270"]={cn:"象征着贰月之神，斯沃西，同时也是园艺之神。",en:"This costume represents Silvosse, the Master of Cuttings and Protector of Flovor."};
descriptions["14271"]={cn:"象征着叁月之神欧谷德。",en:"This costume represents Ulgrude, Protector of Martalo."};
descriptions["14272"]={cn:"象征着肆月之神，哞诺陶中的智者，希罗埃。",en:"This costume represents Silouate, wise Minotoror and Protector of Aperirel."};
descriptions["14273"]={cn:"象征着陆月之神西蒙，他能将食入腹中的任何东西变成珠宝和黄金。",en:"This costume represents Sumens, Protector of Junssidor, who has the unique gift of transforming everything he eats into precious stones and minerals."};
descriptions["14275"]={cn:"象征着玖月之神，恐怖的拉瓦尔。",en:"This costume represents Raval, the terrible Protector of Septangel."};
descriptions["14276"]={cn:"象征着拾壹月之神，冷酷无情的布鲁玛尔。",en:"This costume represents Brumaire, the cold and pitiless Protector of Novamaire."};
descriptions["14277"]={cn:"象征着拾贰月之神，杜约，他也是少有的能毁灭十二世界的恶魔。",en:"This costume represents Djaul, the Protector of Descendre and one of the rare demons able to destroy the World of Twelve."};
descriptions["14278"]={cn:"冷酷如冰，随时准备自我牺牲。",en:"This staff is as cold as ice and is willing to sacrifice... itself."};
descriptions["14279"]={cn:"闪电不会两次劈中同一个地方。",en:"This lightning won\'t strike the same place twice."};
descriptions["14280"]={cn:"象征着伍月之神，鲜花使者洛萨。",en:"This costume represents Rosal, Master of Flowers and Protector of Maysial."};
descriptions["14281"]={cn:"气味芬芳...名字有点傻...",en:"A rose by any other name would smell just as sweet... But you\'re stuck with this stupidly named one now!"};
descriptions["14282"]={cn:"打南边来了个瘸子，担了一挑子茄子，手里拿着个碟子，地下钉着木头橛子。",en:"To help Enutrofs hobble along the Astrub cobbles and prevent wobbling during Gobball squabbles. Now say it over and over again."};
descriptions["14283"]={cn:"这位凶神恶煞的守护神把梅诺的头骨供奉在他的魔杖之上，犹如沉睡的灵魂在在哭号一般让世界都为之颤栗。",en:"The sinister protector enshrined Menalt\'s skull in his staff and a shiver shuddered through the World, as if all the sleeping souls had let out a cry."};
descriptions["14284"]={cn:"象征着杜约的邪恶力量，他是个臭名昭著的恶魔，是魔王的忠实信徒、仆从、爪牙。",en:"This dagger symbolizes all the power of Djaul, infamous demon and disciple, student, and loyal eye of his master, Rushu."};
descriptions["14285"]={cn:"金黄色的闪亮巨剑，在晌午的时候能发挥出它所有的潜能。愿太阳永远照耀着你。",en:"This golden, illuminated sword will unleash its full potential at around midday. It represents the first protector of Javian, Solar. May the sun shine upon you."};
descriptions["14286"]={cn:"象征着叁月的首席护卫，半人马勇士梅诺的擎天之力。",en:"This hammer symbolizes all the power of Menalt, the centaur warrior and first protector of Martalo."};
descriptions["14287"]={cn:"这一称号意味你的心与守护神吉瓦相连。",en:"This title reflects an apparent link with the protector Jiva."};
descriptions["14288"]={cn:"这一称号意味你的心与守护神吉瓦相连。",en:"This title reflects an apparent link with the protector Jiva."};
