descriptions["14354"]={cn:"临终前的最后鼻息，气若游丝，却蕴含着无限魔法。",en:"This final breath is little more than an imperceptible breeze, and yet it contains boundless magic."};
descriptions["14355"]={cn:"用于制造羽毛笔的上佳材料，不断低声诉说着新创意。",en:"A popular feather for making quills, this specimen is just full of creative ideas of its own."};
descriptions["14356"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few drops should suffice."};
descriptions["14357"]={cn:"这种蓝得令人心跳停止的颜色隔着几千里都能清楚地看见。过去在一些战役中，敌人被它吓得直接原地投降了。",en:"This heart-stopping blue can be seen for miles off. In some cases, it\'s enough to make the enemy surrender on the spot."};
descriptions["14358"]={cn:"点击两下来把整组古代资源转换成新的资源。古代资源需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["14359"]={cn:"充满了低声细语，使其很特别。",en:"This metal has been imbued with soft murmurs, which obviously makes it very special."};
descriptions["14360"]={cn:"始终能准确命中目标。传说它的主人在开战之前会低声叮嘱敌人的具体位置。",en:"Whisperers\' lances always find their targets. It\'s said that their owners whisper them detailed directions before they go into battle."};
descriptions["14361"]={cn:"专攻人类敏感部位。",en:"This hand has been trained to jab people in sensitive areas."};
descriptions["14362"]={cn:"踌躇低语者的细小声音不绝于耳。",en:"This pendant echoes with the wispy whispers of lingering Whisperers."};
descriptions["14363"]={cn:"低语者最好的指环。",en:"The best ring by a whisper."};
descriptions["14364"]={cn:"多年来吞噬了无数低语者。现在，让它在你的背包里休养生息吧。",en:"This breastplate has absorbed gallons of whispers over the years. Why not just let it have a rest in your inventory now?"};
descriptions["14365"]={cn:"你整天纳闷，究竟是谁在低声念叨着自己的名字。",en:"This headgear will have you turning in circles trying to figure out who\'s whispering your name."};
descriptions["14366"]={cn:"一阵阵的耳边低语，让你瑟瑟发抖。",en:"Sheathe your body in a spine-tingling whisper."};
descriptions["14367"]={cn:"这份文件授予你\"969年阿玛克纳冠军\"称号。",en:"This document will enable you to prove your status as 969\'s Champion of Amakna."};
descriptions["14368"]={cn:"这份文件授予你\"终极歼灭者\"称号。",en:"This document will enable you to prove your status as Ultimate Exterminator."};
descriptions["14369"]={cn:"这份文件授予你\"机器危机抵抗军\"称号，奖励你在抵抗蒸汽行者入侵战争中的浴血奋斗。",en:"This document will enable you to prove your status as Incessant Fighter of Nano-Dangers, after having repelled the invasion of rebellious Foggernauts."};
descriptions["14370"]={cn:"一张纸从一个蒸汽行者的口袋里掉了出来。上面肯定有重要信息！",en:"Despite their streamlined form, the Foggernauts have pockets too, and this note fell from one of them. Quick, see what it says!"};
descriptions["14371"]={cn:"尽管看起来很机械化，蒸汽行者也是有口袋的。从它的口袋里不小心滑出来了一张纸。快看看上面说了些什么！",en:"Despite their streamlined form, the Foggernauts have pockets too, and this note fell from one of them. Quick, see what it says!"};
descriptions["14372"]={cn:"从蒸汽行者的口袋里飘落的一张纸，上面肯定记载着重要信息！",en:"Despite their streamlined form, the Foggernauts have pockets too, and this note fell from one of them. Quick, see what it says!"};
