descriptions["14416"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["14418"]={cn:"语言来自心灵。",en:"Well I never. Sometimes, words really do come from the heart."};
descriptions["14419"]={cn:"搬运大块鹅卵石的时候肯定会碰到的东西。这中苔藓依附在碎石者上，牢不可分。要找到合适尺寸的化石苔藓很难。",en:"As is to be expected when dealing with what are basically giant boulders, this moss grew on its Crackler and stuck tight. It\'s pretty hard to find decent-sized clumps of it."};
descriptions["14421"]={cn:"保护粗心的低语者免受雪崩突然袭击。",en:"Protects careless Whisperers from sudden avalanches."};
descriptions["14422"]={cn:"让人印象深刻的坐骑，浑身布满健壮有力的肌肉。不要指望它对你撒娇：它会凶猛地噬咬、跺脚，发一整天脾气。",en:"Only a Meridian Star can claim to ride this impressive mount. Its rippling muscles cut an imposing figure."};
descriptions["14423"]={cn:"小小书架，多多知识。",en:"A little bookshelf to hold big knowledge."};
descriptions["14424"]={cn:"点击两下来把整组古代资源转换成新的资源。古代资源需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["14425"]={cn:"用来抵御险恶天气的好材料，让你一抬头满眼青灰色。",en:"All you need to protect against inclement climes and light up the sky with granite gray."};
descriptions["14426"]={cn:"最好还是离它远点。",en:"The expression \'under the thumb\' takes on a new dimension when the thumb in question belongs to a Whispered Crackler."};
descriptions["14427"]={cn:"让人想起一门远古的大炮。威力强大，但是很重。",en:"This bow is somehow reminiscent of a primitive cannon. It\'s powerful, but very heavy."};
descriptions["14428"]={cn:"暴风雨中丝毫不动摇的重盔。",en:"One piece of clothing that should always go down a storm."};
descriptions["14429"]={cn:"像你一样的老道冒险者能用任何破烂抵挡敌人，当然也包括军旗。",en:"A versatile adventurer like you can make heads roll with any old piece of junk, flags included."};
descriptions["14430"]={cn:"前方禁止通行。",en:"Be inapproachable. Rampart Boots."};
descriptions["14431"]={cn:"使你身心坚不可摧。",en:"It protects the body and mind with a single look."};
descriptions["14432"]={cn:"穿着这对肩甲攻击敌人，他们会觉得好像被火车撞到了一样。另一方面来讲，你需要花很多时间才能穿上这对肩甲。",en:"Charge your enemies with these on and they\'ll feel like they\'ve just been run over by a truck. On the other hand, they take so much effort to wear that so will you."};
descriptions["14433"]={cn:"有效防御炮弹攻击。副作用：腹股沟拉伤。",en:"Protects against: cannonballs. Does not protect against: groin strains."};
descriptions["14434"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["14436"]={cn:"被皇室低语诅咒的金属，使其非常受人喜爱。",en:"This metal has been imbued with royal words, which obviously makes it very sought-after."};
descriptions["14437"]={cn:"这把沉重的权杖承载着古代王者的叹息和低语。",en:"This scepter is said to contain the sighs and murmurs of ancient kings."};
descriptions["14438"]={cn:"这份文件授予你\"蒸汽壮劳力\"称号。",en:"This document will enable you to prove your status as Stalwart Foggernaut."};
descriptions["14439"]={cn:"嘿，伙计。它们是有用的，它们在你的双肩上，不断叮嘱你。",en:"Hey dude, they\'ll do; the murmur you need is on your shoulders."};
descriptions["14440"]={cn:"被咒语束缚着的指环，包含所有抗性。",en:"One ring to bring them all and with a murmur bind them."};
descriptions["14441"]={cn:"行走的时候，听得到默默计算步数的声音。",en:"As you walk, these boots count your steps under their breath."};
descriptions["14442"]={cn:"坐在王座上时可以跟它聊聊天。",en:"Finally, someone to talk to when you\'re on the throne."};
descriptions["14443"]={cn:"远古低语者咒语加持，确保穿戴者万无一失。",en:"Its wearer will be protected by the ancient Whisperers\' murmurs."};
descriptions["14444"]={cn:"远古低语者咒语加持，确保穿戴者万无一失。",en:"Its wearer will be protected by the ancient Whisperers\' murmurs."};
