descriptions["14480"]={cn:"一记重击，能让任何木鱼脑袋长眠。",en:"One call for order with this hammer and you\'ll be out stone cold."};
descriptions["14481"]={cn:"碎石者在弓上刻了几个字：我曾经是个冒险者，直到...",en:"The Cracklers tried their hand at writing by carving a few incomprehensible words on this bow: Although this bow poor..."};
descriptions["14482"]={cn:"全方位攻击敌人！",en:"It\'ll drive your enemies ballistic!"};
descriptions["14483"]={cn:"和你的庇护袋十分搭调。虽然很重，但值得拥有。",en:"This looks so good in your home that it\'s definitely worth the weight."};
descriptions["14484"]={cn:"来本地一定要来一杯热腾腾的卡塔普洱！",en:"When you\'re going loco, down a Catapulco!"};
descriptions["14485"]={cn:"开锁专用，童叟无欺。",en:"Apparently this hand has picked hundreds of locks without ever saying a word."};
descriptions["14486"]={cn:"低语者强迫所有的犯人必须穿上这件胸甲。这样一旦他们试图逃跑，从远处就能发现。",en:"The Whisperers make their prisoners wear breastplates like this one so they can be spotted from afar if they make a run for it."};
descriptions["14487"]={cn:"低语声让你很快睡着，或者彻夜不眠。",en:"Will this silky toy lull you to sleep or keep you awake all night?"};
descriptions["14488"]={cn:"最后的遗言，留在旗帜里。",en:"Have the last word in interior design."};
descriptions["14489"]={cn:"哦哦...新鞋子！",en:"Oooh... New shhhoes!"};
descriptions["14490"]={cn:"随风飘扬的一块破布，当备用披风刚刚好。",en:"This well-aired fabric will do just fine as a back-up cloak."};
descriptions["14492"]={cn:"就是这个风格！这种款式是有学习障碍的碎石者设计的，但是它的里面，它的里面！",en:"Such style! It appears to have been designed by a Crackrock with learning difficulties, but if it\'s in, it\'s in!"};
descriptions["14493"]={cn:"享受敌人的悲鸣吧！",en:"The mere sight of it will have your enemies whispering blue murder."};
descriptions["14494"]={cn:"见证了你击败低语者的辉煌历程。",en:"A soft toy to remind you of your glorious victory against the Whisperers."};
descriptions["14495"]={cn:"背信，弃义。为什么恨别人？孩子，回来吧...",en:"You\'re just a traitor boy, so why such a hater, boy, you need to come back down to earth..."};
descriptions["14496"]={cn:"不断细语的饰品，用于装饰庇护袋。放松...",en:"A soft, refined whispering now fills your home. Relax..."};
descriptions["14497"]={cn:"一个美丽的模型，用于广泛地研究如何入侵低语城堡。",en:"A beautiful model that allows for extensive studies on exactly how to invade the Whisperers\' castle."};
descriptions["14498"]={cn:"听说你谋杀了一块岩石还重伤一个石子？不得了啊！",en:"Is it true that you murdered a rock and injured a stone? Woaaaah!"};
descriptions["14499"]={cn:"所以...如果他轻得跟只夸夸一样，那他绝对是个巫师！",en:"So... If he weighs the same as a Quaquack, he\'s definitely a wizard!"};
descriptions["14501"]={cn:"看起来有点古怪，但是能让小孩子们欢乐开怀。",en:"This costume is a bit wacko but pleases the kids."};
descriptions["14502"]={cn:"在南瓜节穿上这件时装，你能更轻易地伪装，不被发现。注意：在一年中的其他日子能起反作用。",en:"Wear this sinister costume on Al Howin\'s night and you should blend into the background to carry out sneaky acts more easily. Note: will have opposite effect on all other days of the year."};
descriptions["14503"]={cn:"起来吧，奴仆。",en:"Get up and ghoul."};
descriptions["14504"]={cn:"诅咒接二连三地显现威力。",en:"The curse will take hold not once but twice!"};
descriptions["14505"]={cn:"现在谁都知道你是坏蛋胚子了。",en:"Now the whole World will know you as the nastiest no-goodnik around."};
descriptions["14506"]={cn:"现在谁都知道你是恶灵召唤者了。",en:"Now the whole World will know you as the Summoner of Evils."};
descriptions["14507"]={cn:"经济实用型的大锅，用于调制毒药、鸡尾酒、魔药以及鲜汤的完美选择。",en:"An economy-size cauldron for brewing insidious poisons, cunning concoctions, lethal potions, and soup."};
descriptions["14508"]={cn:"不咬人的时候是不是显得特别迷人？",en:"Isn\'t it adorable when it doesn\'t bite?"};
descriptions["14509"]={cn:"即便是绵球玩具也无法逃脱南瓜节的诅咒。",en:"Not even this stuffed Gobball has managed to escape Al Howin\'s curse."};
descriptions["14510"]={cn:"没有比塑料蝙蝠球标本更酷的装饰品了。",en:"Nothing says \'I\'m cool\' better than a tree decorated with a plastic Borbat colony."};
descriptions["14511"]={cn:"呃...你还能找到一个比埋这些东西更糟的工作吗？",en:"Uhm... Could you have done a worse job of burying this thing?"};
descriptions["14512"]={cn:"让你的墓穴很时尚，还能防止小鬼们进来打扰。",en:"As well as being frightfully fashionable, it\'ll keep the squatters out of your crypts."};
descriptions["14513"]={cn:"变身低语者。",en:"Whisperers of a feather whisper together."};
descriptions["14519"]={cn:"宠物染料可以于宠物设定介面中更改。此物品已无用处，可以将其分解掉。",en:"Pet colorings can be changed in the pet settings interface. This item is obsolete; you can recycle it."};
descriptions["14520"]={cn:"宠物染料可以于宠物设定介面中更改。此物品已无用处，可以将其分解掉。",en:"Pet colorings can be changed in the pet settings interface. This item is obsolete; you can recycle it."};
