descriptions["14524"]={cn:"你准备选谁作战？",en:"Who will you choose from the Krosmadex?"};
descriptions["14525"]={cn:"整个世界仍然在试图弄清楚它是否与树精森林有关。目前只知道如果你善待它，它会给你惊人的奖励！",en:"The World of Twelve is still trying to determine if this little critter is related to Hel Munster of the erstwhile Treechnid Forest. All that is known is that if you\'re kind enough, it\'ll bring you monstrous bonuses!"};
