descriptions["14527"]={cn:"整个世界仍然在试图弄清楚它是否与树精森林有关。目前只知道如果你善待它，它会给你惊人的奖励！",en:"The World of Twelve is still trying to determine if this little critter is related to Hel Munster of the erstwhile Treechnid Forest. All that is known is that if you\'re kind enough, it\'ll bring you monstrous bonuses!"};
descriptions["14528"]={cn:"告诉全世界你是个狂热收藏家！",en:"Show the World just how much of a collector you are."};
descriptions["14539"]={cn:"好像上面刻着什么东西...如果你能凑近看一眼就好了。",en:"There seems to be something carved on this thing... If only you could take a closer look."};
descriptions["14540"]={cn:"与北方的流行音乐发生共鸣...即便是最困的碎石者也会被吵醒。",en:"This mace resonates with northern pop music - it should be enough to wake up even the sleepiest Cracklers."};
descriptions["14543"]={cn:"卷轴上贴着皇家封印。内容肯定很重要。",en:"This scroll is sealed with the royal stamp. It must say something important."};
descriptions["14545"]={cn:"对于碎语者来说十分珍贵的东西...现在归你了，即便是糖果棒也比它更坚硬。如果你能在尾部粘上更重的东西就好了...",en:"In the Lisper\'s hands, it was capable of mighty things... Now you have it, even a candy cane would thwick and thwack harder. If only you could stick something really heavy on the end..."};
descriptions["14546"]={cn:"细语石碑的复制品。风中回荡着轻声细语。",en:"This copy of a Stele of Murmurs engraving lets off a light rustle in the wind."};
