descriptions["14552"]={cn:"细语石碑的复制品。风中回荡着轻声细语。",en:"This copy of a Stele of Murmurs engraving lets off a light rustle in the wind."};
descriptions["14553"]={cn:"你觉得你比地下城更伟大吗？",en:"Yousa tinken yousa greater dan da dungeons?"};
descriptions["14556"]={cn:"由TNT兄弟制造的烈性炸药！轰！",en:"The famous oil created by brothers Turp and Tyne. It\'s a turp!"};
descriptions["14558"]={cn:"就是一块石头！",en:"Rock on!"};
descriptions["14560"]={cn:"戴上这顶头盔能让所有臭烘烘的绵球臣服于你。",en:"This helmet is supposed to help you get all those pesky Gobballs under your thumb."};
descriptions["14561"]={cn:"可以用来在豆芙群中藏身。很有用，不是吗？",en:"This helmet will make it very easy for you to hide in amongst a group of Tofus. Useful, right?"};
descriptions["14564"]={cn:"柔软丝滑，隐约闻得到一股诱人的烤猪香味。",en:"Soft, silky, and tinged with the lingering scent of caramelized Blibli."};
descriptions["14565"]={cn:"赋予主人强大的嗅觉，找出热腾腾的排泄物的来源。",en:"This helmet will grant its wearer the inimitable power of sniffing out thermal emissions."};
descriptions["14566"]={cn:"这顶头盔表明了佩戴者的身份：甲虫中的VIP！",en:"A helmet like this one gives out a very clear message: I\'m the king of the Scaraleaves, the Scaraleaf VIP!"};
descriptions["14567"]={cn:"能轻易将人闷死。有些人甚至认为这顶头盔就是这么用的。",en:"This helmet is reputed for skewering its victims. Some people go so far as to say it was designed to do just that."};
descriptions["14568"]={cn:"很多人说这顶头盔被冤魂附体。",en:"Many, many people say that this helmet is haunted."};
descriptions["14569"]={cn:"如果你打算独自出发去荒岛，它将是你最佳选择。",en:"This hat might just be your saving grace... if you enjoy solitary excursions to desert islands, that is."};
descriptions["14570"]={cn:"戴上这顶头盔，远离阿玛克纳选美比赛的烦恼！",en:"Pop on this helmet to stop all those Miss Amakna talent scouts from bothering you in the street."};
descriptions["14571"]={cn:"始终让你头脑发热。",en:"A helmet to keep your head at boiling temperature."};
descriptions["14572"]={cn:"抵御严寒的完美选择，厚实温暖。",en:"The perfect extra blanket for the chilly winter ahead."};
descriptions["14573"]={cn:"从披风上的点点血迹来看，它并不能让你飞行。",en:"Judging by the bloodstains all over this cloak, it probably doesn\'t give you the power to fly."};
descriptions["14574"]={cn:"霸气阳刚的披风，告诉咕哩群们谁才是老大。",en:"The musky, masculine odor given off by this cloak will show the Bliblis who\'s boss."};
descriptions["14575"]={cn:"据说能提供完美的伪装，但是好像你已经隐形了。不要在意细节！",en:"I\'d tell you that this cloak is said to provide the perfect camouflage, but you appear to have disappeared. Never mind!"};
descriptions["14576"]={cn:"没有任何东西像它一样坚硬，可以扛得住任何背后的偷袭。",en:"There\'s nothing like a good hard shell on your back to avoid sneaky attacks from behind."};
descriptions["14577"]={cn:"古朴雅致的披风，每个人都想摸一下。这太糟糕了！",en:"A cape so white and pristine that everyone you meet will be tempted to take a tinkle on it. Too bad."};
descriptions["14578"]={cn:"这件披风并不能成为你游手好闲、到处乱逛，把自己装成白骨精的理由。",en:"This is not an excuse to spend the day stalking around pretending to be the king from Game of Bones."};
descriptions["14579"]={cn:"最初用作雨衣。没人可以保证它能不能保护你。",en:"This cape was made to protect itself from the rain. Whether it will protect you too, nobody can guarantee."};
descriptions["14580"]={cn:"使你成为贤明的皇帝。",en:"This cloak will set you on your way to becoming the rightful tsar."};
descriptions["14581"]={cn:"拿来当洗脚布或浴巾的完美选择。",en:"The good thing about this cloak is that you won\'t feel bad about wiping your feet on it or using it to dry your privates after taking a bath."};
descriptions["14582"]={cn:"传说这件披风曾被绵矛革用作门垫。",en:"Legend has it that this cloak was once used by Magmog as a welcome mat."};
descriptions["14583"]={cn:"松软舒适，穿起来后仿佛在云中翩翩起舞。",en:"These epaulettes will have you feeling like you\'re dancing on the clouds."};
descriptions["14584"]={cn:"虽然不够男人味，但是很实用。",en:"These epaulettes are useful if not very manly."};
descriptions["14585"]={cn:"好像有人试穿过这对护肩，这意味着它们曾经很守规矩...",en:"There\'s what looks like an empty fitting on these epaulettes, suggesting that they used to include some kind of mechanism."};
descriptions["14586"]={cn:"太重了，很难穿上，不过很值得穿一件。",en:"Almost too heavy to wear, but so worth it once they\'re on."};
descriptions["14587"]={cn:"戴着这对护肩，你永远不会孤独。",en:"With these epaulettes on your shoulders, you\'ll never walk alone."};
descriptions["14588"]={cn:"如果你是皇家成员，没人在乎你有多丑陋。",en:"If you\'re royal, it doesn\'t matter how ugly you are."};
descriptions["14589"]={cn:"比一般的夹克衫外形更酷，保暖效果更好。",en:"Warmer and cooler than a puffer jacket."};
descriptions["14590"]={cn:"奇怪的是，戒指被唾液覆盖。",en:"Strangely enough, this ring is covered in slobber."};
descriptions["14591"]={cn:"长毛的小戒指。",en:"A hairy little circle."};
descriptions["14592"]={cn:"别怕，它叫起来比打起来狠。",en:"Don\'t worry, its bark is worse than its bite."};
descriptions["14593"]={cn:"带着它你才会明白如何成为一个甲虫。",en:"Wear this ring, and you\'ll understand what it is to be a Scaraleaf."};
descriptions["14594"]={cn:"部落首领值得拥有。",en:"A ring worthy of a tribe leader."};
descriptions["14595"]={cn:"标志着你对于滋滋一族的绝对统治！",en:"A prestigious symbol of your mastery over... the Moskito race!"};
descriptions["14596"]={cn:"只是用血签订的封印契约的标签。",en:"Just the ticket for sealing contracts signed in blood."};
descriptions["14597"]={cn:"内置豆芙妮肖像一张。",en:"There\'s a picture of a Tofoone inside - awww."};
descriptions["14598"]={cn:"为你制作一整年的咕哩薄饼。",en:"This amulet will help you make Blibli blinis all year long."};
descriptions["14599"]={cn:"不可与皮肤直接接触。",en:"Never put this amulet in direct contact with your skin."};
descriptions["14600"]={cn:"一个相当于黄金装备的两倍作用的护符。",en:"An amulet which is twice as efficient as its golden equivalent."};
descriptions["14601"]={cn:"萨弗基亚人相信这根项链能带来好运，因为它在夜晚发出闪闪的红光。当然，这也意味着小偷和杀手在晚上也能毫不费力地找到你。",en:"Sufokians say that this amulet is lucky because it glows in the night. Then again, that does mean that thieves and assassins will never have trouble spotting you."};
descriptions["14602"]={cn:"让人联想到一位著名的刺客。",en:"This amulet is somehow reminiscent of a certain, well-known Sram."};
descriptions["14603"]={cn:"在你的新朋友面前，显得既滑稽又可爱。",en:"This necklace will make you look zany and cool in front of your new friends."};
descriptions["14604"]={cn:"当心，睡着的时候它也会盯着你。",en:"Beware of this amulet. It will watch you when you sleep."};
descriptions["14605"]={cn:"最好的项链也不能让你变漂亮，所以就用便宜货将就下吧。",en:"Not even the finest jewelry could make you look good, so you may as well just wear this cheap tat instead."};
descriptions["14606"]={cn:"值得骄傲的胸甲...挺起你的胸膛！",en:"A breastplate to be proud of - go on, stick out that chest!"};
descriptions["14607"]={cn:"能提供给你的躯干所需的防护。但是不要指望能靠它泡妞...因为它很难看。",en:"This breastplate will offer the protection your torso\'s been waiting for. Just don\'t expect potential suitors to fall at your feet - it is NOT pretty."};
descriptions["14608"]={cn:"现在你们再也不必担心来自身后的偷袭了。",en:"Now you\'re as well protected up front as you are behind."};
descriptions["14609"]={cn:"小心...穿着这件胸甲你会很容易被宝藏猎人盯上。",en:"Careful with this breastplate or you could find yourself targeted by a kama-hungry trapper."};
descriptions["14610"]={cn:"预防蚊虫叮咬，十分有效。",en:"Very effective against Moskito bites."};
descriptions["14611"]={cn:"你懂啥？这就是女王的品味！",en:"Whaddya know? Even queens can have an abominable dress sense."};
descriptions["14612"]={cn:"真有意思。我还以为胸甲上会长出翅膀来...",en:"That\'s funny. I thought there were going to be wings on this breastplate..."};
descriptions["14613"]={cn:"看起来很紧的腰带，系起来之后却觉得自由得像小鸟。",en:"How ironic that the only time you feel as free as a bird is when you\'re strapped tightly into a belt that\'s obviously too small for you."};
descriptions["14614"]={cn:"如果听到饱嗝声，要知道并不一定是从你的胃发出来的。",en:"For once, if you hear gurgling, it\'s probably not coming from your stomach."};
descriptions["14615"]={cn:"所有人都会因为这个腰带上的小翅膀而惊讶。",en:"Everyone wonders what those little wings are all over it."};
descriptions["14616"]={cn:"带着它，保证你不会再变胖了。",en:"At least with this belt, you can be sure you\'ll never get fat."};
descriptions["14617"]={cn:"至少保证一件事：你不会病倒。",en:"This belt should guarantee one thing at least: you won\'t be knocked out by disease."};
descriptions["14618"]={cn:"系上之后让你显得很胖。",en:"A belt that will make you look fat. There, I said it."};
descriptions["14619"]={cn:"当心胃胀气，不小心吹一口气，就会引火烧身。",en:"Beware of careless flatulence; if you play with fire, you\'ll get burned."};
descriptions["14620"]={cn:"把你的脚伸进靴子里之后，你就感觉不到恐惧了。",en:"A little peep of terror escapes these boots as you put your feet in them."};
descriptions["14621"]={cn:"让你双脚闷热！看起来很普通。",en:"These boots will make you feel hot, hot, hot! And look not so hot!"};
descriptions["14622"]={cn:"象牙做的靴子？谁想出来的？炒掉。",en:"Boots made of ivory? Okay, who had this idea? He\'s fired."};
descriptions["14623"]={cn:"十分舒适的靴子，前提是你已经是个死人。",en:"These boots are extremely comfortable, so long as you\'re dead."};
descriptions["14624"]={cn:"用来平衡树桩的最佳选择。",en:"These boots are matchless when it comes to balancing on tree stumps."};
descriptions["14625"]={cn:"主要面向喜欢暴晒脚趾的人群。不用说，市场反响好极了。",en:"Mainly marketed towards those who love tanning their toes but not the rest of their feet. Needless to say, they sell like hotcakes."};
descriptions["14626"]={cn:"如果身后的脚印里带有点点火星，不要觉得太惊讶。",en:"Don\'t worry about the burning embers you leave in your wake - you\'re living the \"hot\" version of Hamster and Gertel!"};
descriptions["14627"]={cn:"能让你成为背上有三颗星的男人。现在，快点趁水果公司还没告你的时候去申请专利吧！",en:"These epaulettes will make a real Samson out of you. Now just make sure you get a patent on them before Api Armor tries to sue you for all you\'ve got."};
descriptions["14629"]={cn:"只有能管理好一个动物园的召唤师才配得上这件盔甲。",en:"Only summoners capable of handling a real menagerie are worthy of wearing this armor."};
descriptions["14630"]={cn:"这个肩甲会帮助成为你同盟中的主力治愈者。",en:"This epaulettes will help you heal your allies like no one else can."};
descriptions["14631"]={cn:"任你千险万阻，我自岿然不动。",en:"This shield will stand triumphant between you and all the dangers of the World of Twelve."};
descriptions["14632"]={cn:"将魔力提升至极限。",en:"A powerful pendant that will help you push your magic powers to the limit."};
descriptions["14633"]={cn:"手指上戴着这么显眼的戒指，没有人会想到你实际上是个穷光蛋。",en:"With this ostentatious sign of wealth on your finger, nobody will ever guess what a measly pauper you are on the inside."};
descriptions["14634"]={cn:"让你奔跑如飞，以至于人们以为是一只瞪羚路过。",en:"These boots will make you run so fast and so effortlessly that people will start mistaking you for a gazelle."};
descriptions["14635"]={cn:"现代制造业的奇迹，经得起各种暴力使用。",en:"This belt is a wonder of modern engineering and has enough room for plenty of snaps, crackles, and pops."};
descriptions["14636"]={cn:"平添不少领袖魅力。一声令下，你忠诚的士兵和军队将会在眨眼之间抵达战场。",en:"This crown will give you buckets of charisma. A cry of \'O come, all ye faithful\' and your army will be there in a flash."};
descriptions["14637"]={cn:"当你的敌人得以靠近欣赏的时候，已经太晚了。",en:"By the time your enemies are close enough to admire the rich colors in this cape, it\'ll be too late for them."};
descriptions["14638"]={cn:"理想的大号镇纸，玩捉迷藏的时候还可以躲在后面。小声点，别吵醒它。",en:"A lovely paperweight and ideal for playing hide-and-seek behind. Just make sure you don\'t shout too loudly around it."};
descriptions["14639"]={cn:"你到底捡了嘘独大师的哪个部位？",en:"It\'s just like that unbearable narcissist to have his organ out in the open for all to see."};
descriptions["14640"]={cn:"你需要至少七个低语者才能举起这片刀锉。但是对于碎石者的大型作业来说十分有用。",en:"You need no fewer than seven Whisperers to handle this file, but it\'s mighty efficient for all those big Crackler jobs."};
descriptions["14641"]={cn:"用于给碎石者最后一击。最棒的是，你只需要四个低语者就能扛起来！",en:"This file is great for putting the finishing touches on Cracklers. Best of all, you only need four Whisperers to carry it!"};
descriptions["14642"]={cn:"直接伤害一般，但是一套拉风的连招可以致敌死地。有点像一刀一刀割伤敌人。",en:"The damage it does may appear pitiful, but a decent combo with this hand can prove fatal. A bit like murder by teaspoon."};
descriptions["14643"]={cn:"低语岛上的岩石，一个舒适的小窝。",en:"Rocks from the Whispering Island make excellent cubbyholes."};
descriptions["14644"]={cn:"曾属于世上最强的时间法师之一。传说他活了很久很久，最后藏在绷带之下的肉体全成了白骨。",en:"This weapon used to belong to one of the World\'s most powerful Xelors. They say he drew out his own life so long that all that remained under his bandages was a brittle skeleton."};
descriptions["14645"]={cn:"据说曾经属于一个皮肤蜡黄，脑袋四方的精灵弓箭手。",en:"This bow is said to have belonged to an elite archer with jaundiced skin and a curiously square head."};
descriptions["14646"]={cn:"所有人都知道查波卡喜欢用弩，却不知道他的表弟弗雷尔喜欢用弓。",en:"Everyone knows that Chowboca fought with a crossbow. A lesser-known fact is that his cousin Freyrr was more into bows."};
descriptions["14647"]={cn:"曾经属于一位治愈者，他的天分太高，名声太大，令人作呕。",en:"This wand used to belong to an Eniripsa so talented and famous that it\'d make you sick to your stomach."};
descriptions["14648"]={cn:"曾经属于一个强大的法师，他能召唤出全身都是棉花糖的恶魔。",en:"This wand used to belong to a powerful sorcerer who could invoke terrible demons made of marshmallow."};
descriptions["14649"]={cn:"当你手里拿着这样一根棍子，不自觉地就会做些滑稽的动作。",en:"A wonderful find for anyone who dabbles in business... Monkey business, that is!"};
descriptions["14650"]={cn:"坚硬的短棍，象征着男子汉的气概、力量和威严。",en:"A very stiff club that symbolizes virility, power, and grandeur."};
descriptions["14651"]={cn:"尺寸并不是最重要的，重要的是你怎么使用它。",en:"You know what they say: it\'s not the size of the tool that matters; it\'s how you use it."};
descriptions["14652"]={cn:"神奇的如意棒，伸长能直插云霄，缩短能塞进口袋。女士最爱。",en:"A magic club which can swell to an impressive size and then shrink again to fit in your pocket. Best appreciated by ladies."};
descriptions["14653"]={cn:"村里的老者们会告诉年轻人，奥古的一根牙签就能毁灭整个村庄。当然这不是真的...",en:"The village elders are fond of telling you youngsters how an entire village was destroyed when Ogrest chucked his toothpick from the mountaintop in a rage. Surely stories like that aren\'t true, though..."};
descriptions["14654"]={cn:"你想多了，这条腿完全不是什么神秘道具，更不能打开什么隐藏奶牛关卡。到底是谁告诉你这些谣言的？",en:"A rumor says that this leg is part of a secret recipe for a potion which will transport you to a Moogrr bonus level. Rumors aren\'t even believable nowadays!"};
descriptions["14655"]={cn:"建议随身携带，以备不时之需。",en:"Keep them in your wallet at all times."};
descriptions["14656"]={cn:"据说邦塔的贵族阿什·加莱什对于卡牌下了诅咒。无论是谁，只要摸到这套牌，就会变成赌徒。",en:"It\'s said that powerful Bontarian nobleman Ush Galesh put a curse on these cards so that whoever used them would become a gambling addict."};
descriptions["14657"]={cn:"用来在鸡尾酒会上制作冰块。显然，有人搞错了用法。",en:"This tool is usually used to make ice cubes for cocktail nights. Some people choose to use it for something entirely different."};
descriptions["14658"]={cn:"好吧，你知道吗？沙皇触角终于派上用处了！",en:"Well, whaddya know? The TsarTsar Horn finally has a use!"};
descriptions["14659"]={cn:"一个没有印章的沙皇就好像没有鼻涕的鼻涕虫！",en:"A tsar without a seal is like a slug without slime!"};
descriptions["14660"]={cn:"属于一位不愿意透露姓名的杀手。他唯一的特征是编号1337，在他的后颈上。黑猫套装没能盖住他的编号。",en:"These legendary daggers belonged to an assassin who never revealed his name. His only distinguishing feature was a tattoo of the number 1337, visible on his neck where his black cat-suit finished."};
descriptions["14661"]={cn:"如果你梦想双刀在手，天下我有，那么你已经达成了一半的目标。小心，它很锋利！",en:"If you\'ve always dreamed of having a twin on each arm, you\'re already halfway there. Careful, it\'s sharp!"};
descriptions["14662"]={cn:"死在剑下的亡魂，缠绕着这把宝剑。",en:"This weapon tingles with the magic it has absorbed from its victims\' souls."};
descriptions["14663"]={cn:"据说它习惯在手下败将的身上划个Z字。也有可能那是个N字。",en:"It\'s used to sign its victims\' torsos with a Z, if the stories are to be believed. Or perhaps that\'s an N."};
descriptions["14664"]={cn:"根据上面刻着的文字，只有十二世界最伟大的守卫才能有权佩戴。",en:"The scriptures say that only the World of Twelve\'s greatest guardian would earn the right to bear this weapon."};
descriptions["14665"]={cn:"轻轻一击就能将敌人打进异次元。",en:"A hammer capable of whacking its target into another dimension."};
descriptions["14666"]={cn:"巨大的宝剑，能将体型巨大的敌人切成汉堡肉。千万别跳瑞士八字舞来庆祝...你的队友会感谢你的。",en:"This enormous sword is efficient at turning even the largest enemies into hamburger meat. Just make sure you don\'t do that swishy figure-of-eight thing to celebrate - your teammates will thank you."};
descriptions["14667"]={cn:"神秘的宝剑，收割在世界中游荡的魔族灵魂。",en:"A mystical sword capable of tailing souls which have spent a little too long in our World."};
descriptions["14668"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["14669"]={cn:"曾经属于一位满脸胡须的神秘勇士，传说他屁股的两边各刻着一个T字纹身。",en:"An imposing blade which once belonged to a mythical, bearded warrior. The rumor goes that he had a T tattooed on each butt cheek."};
descriptions["14670"]={cn:"一把镶了锋利牙齿的斧子，就差一只舌头就能说话了。",en:"An axe studded with sharp little teeth that can rip right through pretty much anything you care to try it out on."};
descriptions["14671"]={cn:"网虫最爱。",en:"The axe of choice for net surfers."};
descriptions["14672"]={cn:"古迦觉得这把斧子能吸引女性。不幸的是，他发现斧子的唯一用途是斩断自己的腋毛。",en:"Grou thought that this would make him irresistible to the ladies. Unfortunately, the only thing he found it useful for was chopping his armpit hair."};
descriptions["14673"]={cn:"你知道我最喜欢什么？蛋糕铲！",en:"You know what I like the most? Cake Shovels!"};
descriptions["14674"]={cn:"没有名字的铲子，献给喜欢这种铲子的人。",en:"For those who like their spades anonymous."};
descriptions["14675"]={cn:"埃努卓不仅贪婪。他也是个有两把刷子的铁匠，据说他创作了很多艺术品。",en:"This Enutrof was not known for his greed alone. He was also an extraordinary blacksmith said to have created many works of art."};
descriptions["14678"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
