descriptions["14695"]={cn:"如果你很幸运的在一件装备上看到这个印章的加盖标志，那么可以肯定的是制作这件装备的男人或女人绝对是个真正意义上了不起的人物。",en:"If you\'re ever lucky enough to see this seal stamped on a piece of equipment, you can be sure that the craftsman who made it is a very great man or woman indeed."};
descriptions["14696"]={cn:"如果你很幸运的在一件装备上看到这个印章的加盖标志，那么可以肯定的是制作这件装备的男人或女人绝对是个真正意义上了不起的人物。",en:"If you\'re ever lucky enough to see this seal stamped on a piece of equipment, you can be sure that the craftsman who made it is a very great man or woman indeed."};
