descriptions["14698"]={cn:"如果你很幸运的在一件装备上看到这个印章的加盖标志，那么可以肯定的是制作这件装备的男人或女人绝对是个真正意义上了不起的人物。",en:"If you\'re ever lucky enough to see this seal stamped on a piece of equipment, you can be sure that the craftsman who made it is a very great man or woman indeed."};
descriptions["14699"]={cn:"开始练习你的皇家派头吧，用不了多久你将加冕为后！",en:"Start practicing your regal wave; you just leveled up on the rags-to-riches scale!"};
descriptions["14700"]={cn:"点击两下来把古代印章转换成新的印章。古代印章需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your Ancient Seal into a new one. Ancient Seals must be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["14701"]={cn:"点击两下来把古代印章转换成新的印章。古代印章需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your Ancient Seal into a new one. Ancient Seals must be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["14702"]={cn:"点击两下来把古代印章转换成新的印章。古代印章需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your Ancient Seal into a new one. Ancient Seals must be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["14703"]={cn:"公主的丑陋护肩。",en:"A haughty look for a naughty crook."};
descriptions["14704"]={cn:"让你想起莱拉公主。",en:"Something about this amulet reminds you of Princess Lela."};
descriptions["14705"]={cn:"让你看起来像个冰柜...呃，也许这是你想要的？",en:"This breastplate makes you look like a wardrobe made of ice. Er... Just what you wanted?"};
descriptions["14706"]={cn:"牢固的腰带，保护你坚实的后背不受伤害。",en:"An uncompromising belt to protect your regal back."};
descriptions["14707"]={cn:"为想成为贵族的人定制。",en:"Made for wannabe noblemen."};
descriptions["14708"]={cn:"愈兽者几乎可以被称作治愈者了，但是同时他也很憧憬成为唤兽师。他大半生都致力于治疗受伤的动物。",en:"Osamost is mostly Eniripsa, but he has a lot of respect for Osamodas too. He spends most of his time healing injured animals."};
descriptions["14709"]={cn:"红龙纳兹天生对于火焰免疫。他的死亡对于世界各地的皮匠是个好消息。",en:"Dracneel developed an incredible resistance to fire during his lifetime. His death was a reason for leather dealers everywhere to celebrate."};
descriptions["14710"]={cn:"卡吉特是幸运猫的忠实拥趸。在村子里，他因为爱猫成痴而闻名。",en:"Kajeet is a big fan of Ecaflip, and he\'s known in his village as the frenzied feline fellow."};
descriptions["14711"]={cn:"看起来像被诅咒了，小偷和劫匪都盯着它。",en:"This amulet seems to be under some kind of curse; thieves and highwaymen can never take their eyes off it."};
descriptions["14712"]={cn:"由一只不识字的笨熊制造，厨师们可以用来做酸奶。",en:"This belt was crafted by a bear with few brain cells and poor spelling."};
descriptions["14713"]={cn:"纪念在布拉克玛地下酒馆里流传着的故事...",en:"A pair of epaulettes created in honor of the legends told in the inns of Brakmar."};
descriptions["14714"]={cn:"冒险者道兹觉得在夜空下和绵球群同眠舒服极了。第二天早晨，人们只找到了这件披风。",en:"This cloak belonged to an adventurer who felt so at one with nature that he decided to sleep with the Gobballs under the night sky. The next morning, only the cloak was found."};
descriptions["14715"]={cn:"使用这把魔杖肯定心情愉悦。看一眼就知道了！",en:"If anything\'s fullabeens, it\'s definitely this wand. I mean, look at it!"};
descriptions["14716"]={cn:"白胡子是个守时的海盗，视财如命。",en:"Whybeard is a punctual pirate who never misses a convoy of kamas."};
descriptions["14717"]={cn:"加里顿是传说中的一位无比勇猛的骑士。他的最爱...安心女士是大地上最漂亮的公主。现实生活中，他们只是两个死宅。",en:"The legend says that Gariden the knight was a brave, brave fellow and that his dearly beloved Anshin was the most ravishing lady in the land. In reality, they were probably just a couple of spotty hicks."};
descriptions["14718"]={cn:"听说了吗？用这把铲子击败兔兔，可以获得额外奖励。不过也许这是瞎话。",en:"You\'ve heard it said that this shovel bears a Wodent-killing bonus. But it\'s probably nonsense."};
descriptions["14719"]={cn:"自从有个和尚躲进螃蟹壳之后，他就潜心采集螃蟹腮毛，编织成了这顶腥臭的头盔。",en:"After leaving has-been boy band Hansum, Yke the Cwab Slayer set up shop selling malodorous helmets."};
descriptions["14720"]={cn:"赫拉姆十分崇拜布丁时尚。从一个人的爱好里我们可以看出他的品味...",en:"Heram simply adooored Puddly fashion, which should tell you a lot about Heram as a person."};
descriptions["14721"]={cn:"冒险者布鲁斯特以其...恩...令人难忘的气味闻名于世。",en:"Blust the adventurer is best known for... well... his unforgettable odor."};
descriptions["14722"]={cn:"使用最新科技，为你省下大量龙鸟卡米。",en:"These boots use the best of modern technology to save you hundreds and hundreds of Dragoturkey kamiles."};
descriptions["14723"]={cn:"早晨起床真开心，哦哈哟！呀达！",en:"A ring to cheer up any dreary morning. Ohayouuu!"};
descriptions["14724"]={cn:"天知道原来可爱的莱拉公主有个名字相近的伙伴。",en:"So it turns out that gracious Princess Lela had a homonym all this time! Who knew?"};
descriptions["14725"]={cn:"曾被叫做糊糊戒指。自从辛维尔在烂泥堆中浴血奋战之后，就以他的名字命名了。",en:"This ring used to be called the Mushd Ring, but Synwel used to finish fights so muddy that it was renamed in his honor."};
descriptions["14726"]={cn:"只是一件普通的石笋制品。",en:"Just your average Stalagmote bling."};
descriptions["14727"]={cn:"据说一位著名的鲨鱼猎手神秘失踪了...根据你找到这对护肩的地方来看，能推测出他已经...",en:"A famous Shark hunter reported missing in mysterious circumstances... Judging by the place you found these epaulettes, the mystery is solved."};
descriptions["14728"]={cn:"莱雅，我是你的...",en:"Leia, I am your..."};
descriptions["14729"]={cn:"福莱达很喜欢蜘蛛，她决定穿得和蜘蛛一样，和蜘蛛一同生活。蜘蛛们最终决定吸纳她为新的族人。",en:"Frida loved Arachnees so much that she decided to dress like one and go and live with them. The Arachnees eventually adopted her as one of their own."};
descriptions["14730"]={cn:"这枚结婚戒指包含了格里德纳最深的感情，是送给挚爱的最佳选择。",en:"This wedding ring contains Gridena\'s deepest sentiments. What better gift for your sweetheart?"};
descriptions["14731"]={cn:"显然，香宇曾经拿这把刻着星星的匕首当飞刀用。现在已经有明令禁止类似的游戏。",en:"Apparently, Xiangu used to use this star-studded dagger as a throwing knife. These days, there are laws against that kind of thing."};
descriptions["14732"]={cn:"卢申是世上最强的狼之一。但是再强的狼也敌不过时间的推移，现在这件披风属于你了。",en:"Luccian was one of the World\'s most powerful Boowolves. But not even a Boowolf can tether the ravages of time, and now the cloak is yours."};
descriptions["14733"]={cn:"戒指内圈刻着一行字：钻石恒久远，一颗不流传。",en:"There\'s an engraving on this ring: \"Brimful of Ashal on the 55. Well it\'s a brimful of Ashal on the 55.\" What kind of lousy mantra is that?!"};
descriptions["14734"]={cn:"献给老鼠和有志成为老鼠的家伙...",en:"This belt is highly prized by Rats and wannabe Rats."};
descriptions["14735"]={cn:"曾属于一位瓦格纳城堡的守卫。",en:"This helmet used to belong to a guard at Wagnar\'s castle."};
descriptions["14736"]={cn:"失踪已久的守护者古盾。",en:"The ancestral shield of a long-lost Feca."};
descriptions["14737"]={cn:"用来展示你最喜欢的时装，时尚万岁！",en:"An incredible fashion dummy to proudly display your loveliest sets, costumes and insignia. You\'re set for life!"};
descriptions["14738"]={cn:"用来展示你最喜欢的时装，时尚万岁！",en:"An incredible fashion dummy to proudly display your loveliest sets, costumes and insignia. You\'re set for life!"};
descriptions["14740"]={cn:"假设这也算是盔甲，可它实在保护不了什么。话说回来，穿着倒确实很性感！",en:"Granted, this armor won\'t really protect you from enemy attacks. You gotta admit, though, it does look pretty sexy!"};
descriptions["14741"]={cn:"有只兔兔缠在你的腰上？哇哦，放松点，现在流行这个！",en:"A Wodent \'round your pelvis? Woah, take it easy, hot stuff!"};
descriptions["14742"]={cn:"每个人都梦想拥有兔兔指环。",en:"Who hasn\'t dreamed of having a Wodent ring on their finger?"};
descriptions["14743"]={cn:"阿宅必备。穿上它们，去任何地下城都好像在家里一样舒适。",en:"These slippers are perfect for stay-at-home adventurers. Slip them on and you\'ll feel right at home in any dungeon in the World of Twelve."};
descriptions["14744"]={cn:"也就暖暖头用。",en:"A hat that will keep its wearer\'s assets warm."};
descriptions["14745"]={cn:"千万不要相信兔脚会带来好运...",en:"You\'d have to be really naive to believe a Wodent foot could bring good luck..."};
descriptions["14746"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["14750"]={cn:"你努力让自己朝着冠军的方向迈进，做的好！",en:"You managed to scribe yourself into this title. Well done!"};
descriptions["14751"]={cn:"对于烤熟的栗子，你一点办法也没有。",en:"You just can\'t beat a roasted Chastenut."};
descriptions["14752"]={cn:"摸一摸，闻一闻。适度使用。",en:"Scratch and sniff. Use in moderation."};
descriptions["14753"]={cn:"啊！我的眼睛！",en:"Don\'t it make your brown eyes sting?!"};
descriptions["14754"]={cn:"这块新鲜的肉令人食指大动，肉质鲜嫩可口。好吧...只要你烹调得法，确实很好吃。",en:"This hunk of fresh meat will taste just as good as it looks. Well... Once you\'ve prepared it, that is!"};
descriptions["14755"]={cn:"传说曾经有一名丧心病狂的时间法师在烤龙鸟的时候，弄丢了自己的手表。",en:"Legend says that a daft Xelor once lost his watch preparing a Stuffed Dragoturkey."};
descriptions["14756"]={cn:"蒸汽行者和南瓜：两个主旨二选一。你是十二世界中为数不多值得这个头衔的居民。",en:"Foggernauts and Al Howin: the two themes of choice. You\'re one of the rare inhabitants in the World of Twelve worthy of this title!"};
descriptions["14757"]={cn:"现在你能做出世界上最好吃的烤龙鸟了。",en:"With this recipe, you\'ll be inclined to shout obscenities, but will cook the most delicious roast Dragoturkey known to man."};
descriptions["14759"]={cn:"打开包裹，数数里面的礼物吧！",en:"Open this pouch and behold the gift within!"};
