descriptions["14811"]={cn:"这份文件授予你\"竞技场冠军\"称号。",en:"This document will enable you to prove your status as Champion of the Arena."};
descriptions["14812"]={cn:"如果你梦想双刀在手，天下我有，那么你已经达成了一半的目标。小心，它很锋利！",en:"If you\'ve always dreamed of having a twin on each arm, you\'re already halfway there. Careful, it\'s sharp!"};
descriptions["14813"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。（包含两把相似的匕首）",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
