descriptions["14819"]={cn:"十二世界中唯一能用来挖掘宝藏的铲子。",en:"One of the only shovels in the World of Twelve that you can use to dig up buried treasure."};
descriptions["14820"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few drops should suffice."};
descriptions["14821"]={cn:"只要你觉得和异种虫卵同眠也没关系，那么就放心把这件披风当棉被好了。",en:"You\'re welcome to use this cloak as a quilt, as long as you like sharing the bed. With larva hatchlings."};
descriptions["14822"]={cn:"内壁厚厚的胶质层使这款帽子一码通用。",en:"This hat is one-size-fits-all. The thick mucus all around the inside makes sure of that."};
descriptions["14823"]={cn:"在下雨的时候，主宰用这对护肩作为新生幼虫的庇护所。",en:"The Shin Larva used to use these epaulettes as little shelters for the new hatchlings when it was due to rain."};
descriptions["14824"]={cn:"舒适的胸甲。臭气熏人，牢牢粘在你的皮肤上，还不能水洗。",en:"This breastplate is really comfortable. Too bad it stinks, it\'s sticky, and you can\'t put it in the wash."};
descriptions["14825"]={cn:"鞋子的底部由变异幼虫残肢制成的。你在阿斯图布闲逛的同时，也能享受免费足底按摩。",en:"The soles of these boots are made of baby larvae. Now you\'ll have a free foot massage to make your walks around Astrub nice and relaxing."};
descriptions["14826"]={cn:"廉价的压力小球，有点恶心。",en:"A cheap, if disgusting, stress ball."};
descriptions["14827"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["14828"]={cn:"有时候你放进包里的东西甚至会让你自己恶心。",en:"Sometimes, the things you keep in your bag disgust even you."};
descriptions["14829"]={cn:"自从主宰有一次被蜜蜂蛰了屁股之后，它就变得小心翼翼。它睡觉的时候都握着这柄剑，随时准备战斗。",en:"After being stung once in its behind by a bee, the Shin Larva took desperate measures. This sword is alert and on the attack at all times."};
descriptions["14830"]={cn:"将你心爱之人永远留在身边...",en:"This could be just the thing to keep your dearly beloved by your side forever... and ever... and ever..."};
descriptions["14831"]={cn:"我们都在考虑同一件事，但是我们确实很羞于启齿：身上的某个重要位置被这种黏糊糊的东西糊住真的让人很不爽。",en:"We\'re all thinking it, but we\'re too shy to say it out loud: on certain parts of the body, this gooey viscosity isn\'t so unpleasant"};
descriptions["14832"]={cn:"很粘很恶心，一旦上身就脱不下来。",en:"You made a good choice turning that Strich into epaulettes rather than nuggets. they\'re Viscous Epaulettes and now they won\'t come off!"};
descriptions["14835"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["14836"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["14837"]={cn:"如果护符坏了，那是因为乌鸦整天在树皮上又啄又扯的缘故。",en:"If this amulet is in bad condition, blame the Crobaks that spend their days pecking and tearing at Treechnids\' bark."};
descriptions["14838"]={cn:"使用远古树精天然树脂拼接而成。虽然经常会黏住一些小虫子，但是质地坚韧。",en:"This cape was put together using the Ancestral Treechnid\'s natural sap. It\'s always getting fluff stuck in its cracks, but at least it\'s solid."};
descriptions["14839"]={cn:"但愿远古树精的树皮比它的牙齿坚硬。",en:"Let\'s hope the Ancestral Treechnid\'s bark is stronger than his bite."};
descriptions["14840"]={cn:"戒指不错...从客观角度来讲。你戴起来漂亮极了。我可不想要，可是你戴确实不错...",en:"This ring is nice... I mean, in an understated way. It looks good on you. I wouldn\'t wear one myself, but you know..."};
descriptions["14841"]={cn:"大象莱尼要发疯了...！她刚把那堆树干包裹妥当，而你却把它戴在了头上！",en:"Lenny the Elephant is going to be so mad...! She\'d only just packed that trunk and now you\'ve got it on your head!"};
descriptions["14842"]={cn:"大多数靴子刚穿起来的时候都有点硌脚，但是穿这双靴子却像在脚上插了一根荆棘刺！看来你必须忍受折磨才能成为真英雄。",en:"Most boots hurt a bit until they\'re worn in, but these ones will be a thorn in your side all the time! Sometimes you just have to suffer to be a hero."};
descriptions["14843"]={cn:"喜欢住在你的脚趾缝里。",en:"These Grains of Sand fit nicely in between your toes, in all your nooks and crannies, and in your sandwiches."};
descriptions["14845"]={cn:"远古树精的最后残留...你手中握着的，是历史残片。",en:"This bark is one of the last existing pieces of the Ancestral Treechnid... You\'re holding a piece of history in your hands."};
descriptions["14846"]={cn:"谁能想得到这根漂亮的多彩羽毛来自一只信天翁的下体？",en:"Who would have thought this beautiful, multicolored feather came from an Albatrocious\'s nether regions?"};
descriptions["14847"]={cn:"如果你想好好保留这些珍珠，记得千万别让尼娜·瑞卡发现。她会毫不犹豫地从你手里抢走珍珠！",en:"If you don\'t want to cast your pearls before swine, you\'ll need to keep this far from Nina Richa. She won\'t think twice before trying to snatch it from your mitts!"};
descriptions["14850"]={cn:"据说制弓的缠丝蜘蛛来回拉扯了五十九次弓弦，直到远古树精满意为止。",en:"They say the Arachnee Embroiderer who strung this bow had to start from scratch fifty-nine times before the Ancestral Treechnid was satisfied with it."};
descriptions["14851"]={cn:"用最牢的木头制成。知道它为什么坚不可摧了吧？",en:"This shield is crafted using the sturdiest wood around. That\'s what makes it so resistant to attacks."};
descriptions["14852"]={cn:"只有一种尺码。瘦子们必须拽紧他们的裤子，而胖子们必须...减肥。",en:"This belt is available in one size only. Skinny malinkeys will have to hold it up, whilst fatties can... well, lose some weight."};
descriptions["14853"]={cn:"腰带的最初版本不太牢固。重新用树精枝叶加工了一下，现在你再也不用担心裤子会掉下来了。",en:"The original version of this belt wasn\'t very solid. It\'s been remade with Treechnid branches so its wearer won\'t end up with his pants around his ankles."};
descriptions["14854"]={cn:"你只需要一只卷笔刀，就能让这把匕首变成令敌人胆寒的武器。",en:"All you need to make this weapon a fearsome battle companion is a decent pencil sharpener."};
descriptions["14855"]={cn:"由潮木制成。潮木比普通木头稍差，戴起来像个小水桶。",en:"This amulet was made with damp wood. Damp wood isn\'t more powerful than ordinary wood; it just happened to be raining buckets."};
descriptions["14856"]={cn:"用一块木头去砍伐另一块木头...你不觉得很讽刺吗？",en:"Chopping wood with wood... Isn\'t that ironic? Dontcha think?"};
descriptions["14857"]={cn:"前往地下城门口的兑奖机处兑换酷炫的奖励。",en:"Use the machine across from the dungeon to exchange your tokens for fantastic rewards."};
descriptions["14859"]={cn:"头盔上的羽毛立刻让你变身为本地人。现在你得以以贵宾身份参加岛上的任何狂欢派对！",en:"The feathers on this headgear will have you looking like one of the natives in no time. You\'ve now got yourself a VIP pass to all the wicked island parties they throw!"};
descriptions["14860"]={cn:"这对肩甲由金刚鹦鹉的两片长喙制成，一边一只。你终于让那些鸟闭上嘴了！",en:"This hunting trophy is embellished with two fine Macawker beaks, one on each shoulder. So you finally managed to shut them up!"};
descriptions["14861"]={cn:"鲜艳的颜色始终提醒着你：你是来度假的！这一两周内别再想搬砖了...",en:"This cloak\'s bright colors will remind you just why you\'re here: for a holiday! No more working for a week or two..."};
descriptions["14862"]={cn:"哇哦。当你一开始说你想当摇摆舞之王、岛屿贵宾的时候，没有人想到你会穿成这样。",en:"Wow. When you said you wanted to be king of the swingers now, the island VIP, nobody expected it to be so... graphic."};
descriptions["14863"]={cn:"你闻到了鱼腥味吗？",en:"Can you smell fish?"};
descriptions["14864"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["14867"]={cn:"纪念你击败船长的光辉事迹。",en:"A squid pro quo for your triumph over the Captain."};
descriptions["14872"]={cn:"在你戴上它上战场之前请确认你已经清洗过了，因为鸟粪的味道绝对不会给你留下什么好的回忆。",en:"Make sure you give this breastplate a wipe before you charge into battle; guano really doesn\'t give off a good impression."};
descriptions["14873"]={cn:"如果你觉得穿高跟鞋很难走路，试试这双靴子。现在你知道蟹行有多难了。",en:"If you thought high heels were hard to walk in, try these Cwabettos! Now you know why the crab walk looks so painfully awkward."};
descriptions["14874"]={cn:"被海星咬到手指了！该死的海星！",en:"Starlie bit your finger! Ouch, Starlie!"};
descriptions["14875"]={cn:"穿上，开始搞怪！",en:"Try on these epaulettes and get your freak on!"};
descriptions["14878"]={cn:"镶嵌着一个骷髅头，让你看起来像追风少年。",en:"Embellished with a skull to give you the bad-boy look you\'ve been coveting so."};
descriptions["14879"]={cn:"经过了艰苦卓绝的诉讼，品牌所有人光耀集团终于可以为自己正名。可是竞争对手的绿色斧子依然很畅销。",en:"After a long and difficult struggle with the patenting office, this axe finally gained the right to bear its name proudly. Its rival was renamed to Tropilax and is still the best-selling medication on Calamari Island."};
descriptions["14880"]={cn:"我们并不太熟悉这把魔杖的由来。只知道那里的人说着一种叫做“沙维什”的难懂语言。",en:"We don\'t know much about this wand other than the people from its lands speak an incomprehensible language known as \"Chavish.\""};
descriptions["14881"]={cn:"贝壳制成的卡牌。用来在沙滩上斗地主，输掉的时候可以尽情发泄。",en:"A set of cards made of stray shells. Perfect for playing on the beach, and slitting a throat or two when you lose."};
descriptions["14882"]={cn:"带有扣带，防止水手在甲板上摔个狗啃泥。",en:"These boots have a good grip on them to stop the seamen falling flat on their faces."};
descriptions["14883"]={cn:"一根旧绳索制成的水手腰带。外观普普通通，但是结实耐用。",en:"A sailor belt made from a length of old rope. It\'s not fancy, but it\'ll do the job."};
descriptions["14884"]={cn:"这件胸甲实在太寒碜了，用来假装在海难中幸存的船员倒是很合适，有船走过记得呼救。",en:"This breastplate is so battered and worn that you could easily pretend to be a shipwreck survivor and cadge a lift off a friendly ship."};
descriptions["14885"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["14886"]={cn:"标记着乌贼船长的藏宝图的精确位置！大概在20步左右那里。注意：一旦使用，指南针只能使用一次。",en:"This compass will mark out the exact spot of Calamari\'s hidden treasure map! Well, within 20 paces or so. Careful: the compass will be demagnetized by its first use."};
descriptions["14887"]={cn:"尽管是个话痨，但是会衷心诚意地跟着你到天涯海角！",en:"Although a bit too chatty, this Macawker will accompany you anywhere as discreetly as he is able!"};
descriptions["14888"]={cn:"他们说你永远也找不到珍珠戒指，很明显他们错了。下一步，找个美人鱼做新娘！",en:"They said you\'d never find a Pearlfriend, but you proved them wrong! Next up, a whale-order bride!"};
descriptions["14889"]={cn:"你需要练习良久才能把这根毛用掌风吹起来，尤其是逆风的时候。",en:"It\'ll take a fair bit of training before you can chuck this hand further than a meter or so, especially if the wind\'s not in your favor."};
descriptions["14890"]={cn:"为初学者精心设计。",en:"This ring is made for tearful novices. It also symbolizes some ancient, unspeakable traditions. It\'s made for you! Perfect."};
descriptions["14891"]={cn:"怀表在手，寻宝无忧。",en:"With this shiny amulet on your side, you\'ll never have trouble finding rare items again."};
descriptions["14892"]={cn:"就是它了！百分百酷洛大师主题的庇护袋！所有酷洛英雄都在这里！",en:"With this kit, you can have a 100% Krosmaster-themed Haven Bag! The Krosmoz\'s greatest heroes!"};
descriptions["14893"]={cn:"这张桌子像一些蘑菇那样又大又平，也许是萨迪达神照着自己的样子铸造的。",en:"Some mushrooms are so big and so flat that you\'d think the god Sadida had molded them to match the form of his generous behind."};
descriptions["14894"]={cn:"宠物染料可以于宠物设定介面中更改。此物品已无用处，可以将其分解掉。",en:"Pet colorings can be changed in the pet settings interface. This item is obsolete; you can recycle it."};
descriptions["14895"]={cn:"宠物染料可以于宠物设定介面中更改。此物品已无用处，可以将其分解掉。",en:"Pet colorings can be changed in the pet settings interface. This item is obsolete; you can recycle it."};
