descriptions["14897"]={cn:"宠物染料可以于宠物设定介面中更改。此物品已无用处，可以将其分解掉。",en:"Pet colorings can be changed in the pet settings interface. This item is obsolete; you can recycle it."};
descriptions["14898"]={cn:"宠物染料可以于宠物设定介面中更改。此物品已无用处，可以将其分解掉。",en:"Pet colorings can be changed in the pet settings interface. This item is obsolete; you can recycle it."};
descriptions["14899"]={cn:"宠物装备可以于宠物设定介面中更改。此物品已无用处，可以将其分解掉。",en:"Pet equipment can be changed in the pet settings interface. This item is obsolete; you can recycle it."};
descriptions["14900"]={cn:"宠物装备可以于宠物设定介面中更改。此物品已无用处，可以将其分解掉。",en:"Pet equipment can be changed in the pet settings interface. This item is obsolete; you can recycle it."};
descriptions["14901"]={cn:"宠物装备可以于宠物设定介面中更改。此物品已无用处，可以将其分解掉。",en:"Pet equipment can be changed in the pet settings interface. This item is obsolete; you can recycle it."};
descriptions["14902"]={cn:"宠物装备可以于宠物设定介面中更改。此物品已无用处，可以将其分解掉。",en:"Pet equipment can be changed in the pet settings interface. This item is obsolete; you can recycle it."};
descriptions["14904"]={cn:"拥有强大魔力...但是佩戴者的动作会变慢。",en:"This magic amulet holds impressive power... but wearing it will slow down its bearer\'s actions."};
descriptions["14905"]={cn:"粘乎乎的，习惯了之后你会觉得自在舒适。",en:"The stickiness can be unnerving, but your feet will feel as snug as a bug in a rug in these boots."};
descriptions["14906"]={cn:"如果我有翅膀，我就能飞。我有翅膀吗？没有，但是我有这件披风，所以我就变成蝴蝶飞给你看。",en:"This cloak is a major step on your way to becoming a butterfly."};
descriptions["14907"]={cn:"这顶帽子只能用来做两件事：展示婴幼儿产品或者收集阿斯图布的花粉。",en:"There are only two things you can do with this hat: model for baby catalogs or collect pollen in Astrub."};
descriptions["14908"]={cn:"为双肩遮风挡雨的理想选择。",en:"An outright honorable place to stow away your dignified shoulders."};
descriptions["14909"]={cn:"你看起来像个忙碌的大黄蜂。至少现在，变异虫群会将你视为首领。",en:"You look like a busy, buzzy bumblebee. At least now the Larvae will worship you the way you always dreamed they would."};
descriptions["14910"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["14911"]={cn:"在放进庇护袋之前别忘了把里面的东西掏空。否则到处滋生的变异虫会毁了你的菜地！",en:"Don\'t forget to empty it out thoroughly before you set it up in your home. Those little larvae will run riot in your vegetable patch!"};
descriptions["14912"]={cn:"无须修剪浇水。",en:"This little shrub doesn\'t even need to be trimmed or watered."};
descriptions["14913"]={cn:"无须修剪浇水。",en:"This little shrub doesn\'t even need to be trimmed or watered."};
descriptions["14914"]={cn:"在嘘独王国阴森的矿洞里十分有用。",en:"A Whisperer\'s pick that\'s essential for all the most meticulous excavations in Shhhudoku\'s Kingdom."};
descriptions["14915"]={cn:"诱人的小瓶子里装着一张假藏宝图。那帮贪婪的蠢海盗已经忘了那个叉的意义了。",en:"This tempting bottle contains a fake treasure map. Those greedy numskulls have forgotten that X never, ever marks the spot!"};
descriptions["14916"]={cn:"砰砰砰！噢噢！",en:"Boing, boing, boing, boing, bonk, OW!"};
descriptions["14917"]={cn:"大多数植物术士睡地上。你知道，抠脚汉做不了公主。",en:"Most Sadidas just sleep on the ground, you know. You can\'t live like a princess AND bite your own toenails."};
descriptions["14918"]={cn:"没有耐心的知识就像是点不亮的蜡烛。\n- 艾萨·梅萨·牛顿爵士",en:"Knowledge without patience is like a candle without a flame. -Isaa Meesa Newton Sir"};
descriptions["14919"]={cn:"那天，我偶然看见一个和我长得一模一样的布娃娃，她的背上插着一根针。从那以后，我的背后总是痒痒的！",en:"This one time, I ran into a doll which looked just like me, but it had a needle sticking out of its back. And ever since, my back has been sooo itchy!"};
descriptions["14920"]={cn:"丰满的萨迪达少女偶尔也需要含蓄一下。",en:"Perfect for buxom Sadidas who want to retain their modesty."};
descriptions["14921"]={cn:"布拉克玛国民十分熟悉这种植物。它散发出的雄性气味能吸引贝拉。",en:"Brakmarians are familiar with this kind of plant. The male pheromones it secretes attract Bellaphones."};
descriptions["14922"]={cn:"塞满了一堆苔藓、短裤以及长满了苔藓的短裤。",en:"These drawers are full of moss, underpants, and mossy underpants."};
descriptions["14923"]={cn:"游戏只有一条规则：越湿越好！",en:"This game only has one rule: wetter iiiis better!"};
descriptions["14924"]={cn:"对植物术士来说，没有比阴暗潮湿的行军橱更适合存放脆弱的植物了。",en:"What better place to store fragile plants than in a dark and musty wardrobe?"};
descriptions["14925"]={cn:"刺客们只是随便买了个二手的桌子，反正再漂亮的桌子都要沾上厚厚的一层血迹。",en:"Srams are just as well buying second-hand tables, because they only go and cover them in bloodstains right from the start anyway."};
descriptions["14926"]={cn:"爷爷以前有一句口头禅：教骑士，等于教了一堆空气。而教会了刺客，你就教会了整整一个家族。",en:"As grandpa used to say: \'Teach a Iop and you teach no-one. Teach a Sram and you teach a whole family.\'"};
descriptions["14927"]={cn:"刺客不会在床上睡很久，他们坚信“死了之后就醒不过来了”。确实很有道理。",en:"Srams don\'t spend much time in bed; they believe they can \"sleep when they\'re dead.\" That\'s one way of looking at it."};
descriptions["14928"]={cn:"刺客（睡得很少，你懂的）利用夜晚的灯光练习影分身术，整条大街都是他们的残影。这群混蛋！",en:"Srams (who, as you know, don\'t sleep much) use this night-light to practice casting spooky shadows for when they creep from back street to back street. Those felons!"};
descriptions["14929"]={cn:"那天，我发现了一个斯拉姆吉祥物，很明显是从一个倒楣的刺客身上抢来的。真讽刺！",en:"This one time, I found a Sram mascot that had obviously been robbed from an unfortunate Sram. And that\'s sooo ironic!"};
descriptions["14930"]={cn:"想知道屏风后面藏着什么？走，去看看，你先上。说了你先上！",en:"Want to know what\'s hidden behind this screen? Go and have a look. You first; I insist."};
descriptions["14931"]={cn:"植物死了之后，种子可以用来制造大规模杀伤性毒药。",en:"Once this plant is dead, its seeds can be used to make a wide range of insidious poisons."};
descriptions["14932"]={cn:"奶奶经常说“匕首在手，天下我有”。",en:"As grandma used to say: \'Dagger in hand, cunning disguise, make a Sram healthy, wealthy, and wise.\'"};
descriptions["14933"]={cn:"刺客心跳是个经典的游戏。",en:"Pinball Sramble is an old classic."};
descriptions["14934"]={cn:"当你伸手进去取围巾的时候，当心别被刀锋、碎玻璃和各种小机关弄伤。里面的东西足够让你吓一跳！",en:"When you reach in to grab your scarf, be careful of the blades, broken glass, and booby traps hidden inside. It\'s enough to give you the shivers!"};
descriptions["14935"]={cn:"如果有治愈者请你喝茶，请别多虑，人家只是好客嘛...对吧...肯定不会拿你当实验品的，放心。",en:"If an Eni invites you in for tea, don\'t read too much into it; he\'s probably just nice like that... Although... No, wait. There\'s definitely something funny going on."};
descriptions["14936"]={cn:"这个漂亮的首饰盒一定装着什么贵重的东西！该死，只有阿司匹林。生活真无聊！",en:"This beautiful box must contain something lovely! Oh, just aspirin. Life is so disappointing! Hmmm..."};
descriptions["14937"]={cn:"睡吧，睡觉能治愈你心灵的创伤...",en:"To sleep, perchance to heal - ay, there\'s the ointment... Willum Acheseer"};
descriptions["14938"]={cn:"路上看到了小治愈者的话，就捡回家吧，她能带给你一整天的好运。把她绑在灯台上，她能让你好运常在。",en:"See an Eni, pick it up, all day long you\'ll have good luck; have the Eni fit a light, the good luck will keep you right."};
descriptions["14939"]={cn:"那天，我把安妮丽莎吉祥物当成了兔兔拖鞋。穿起来舒服极了！",en:"This one time, I confused an Eniripsa charm just like this one for a pair of Wodent Slippers. And it was sooo comfortable!"};
descriptions["14940"]={cn:"有没有比躲在屏风后面洗澡更糟的事？有，在屏风前面洗澡。",en:"The only thing worse than making love behind a screen is not making love behind a screen."};
descriptions["14941"]={cn:"它们被称作天选之花。没有人知道为什么它们那么漂亮，当然也没有人在乎。",en:"These are known as the Flowers That Be. Nobody\'s really sure why their existence in itself is so impressive, but nobody really cares either."};
descriptions["14942"]={cn:"仔细看看，这可是治愈者在闺房里用的哦。",en:"Take a good, long look. This is the closest you\'ll ever get to an Eni\'s chest or drawers."};
descriptions["14943"]={cn:"来自一个完全不同的时代。根据古书记载，它的名字叫做头牌病号。也许在装订线的边缘抄错了几个字。",en:"This games table comes from a whole other era. According to the old manuscripts, it\'s called Top-a-Patient, although there was probably a transcription error somewhere along the line."};
descriptions["14944"]={cn:"行军橱里装有血液样本、尿液样本、汗液样本以及其他不知名的样本，甚至还有水蛭。万全的准备！",en:"This Eniripsa Wardrobe contains blood samples, urine samples, sweat samples, unspeakable samples, and leeches. Talk about being prepared!"};
descriptions["14947"]={cn:"12枚硬币，因爱铸就。",en:"12 little kamas, minted with love."};
descriptions["14948"]={cn:"16枚硬币，因爱铸就。",en:"16 little kamas, minted with love."};
descriptions["14949"]={cn:"20枚硬币，因爱铸就。",en:"20 little kamas, minted with love."};
descriptions["14950"]={cn:"100枚硬币，因爱铸就。",en:"100 little kamas, minted with love."};
descriptions["14951"]={cn:"6,000枚硬币，因爱铸就。",en:"6,000 little kamas, minted with love."};
descriptions["14952"]={cn:"500枚硬币，因爱铸就。",en:"500 little kamas, minted with love."};
descriptions["14966"]={cn:"虽然你感觉鞋里闷热得像烤炉，但是柔软潮湿的靴子内衬让足部皮肤全天保持滋润。",en:"Even though you might feel like you\'re walking on flan, the supple and humid texture of these boots will keep your skin feeling well-hydrated all day long."};
descriptions["14968"]={cn:"虽然你感觉鞋里闷热得像烤炉，但是柔软潮湿的靴子内衬让足部皮肤全天保持滋润。",en:"Even though you might feel like you\'re walking on flan, the supple and humid texture of these boots will keep your skin feeling well-hydrated all day long."};
descriptions["14970"]={cn:"让你看起来像蓝色战士，恐虫战队的成员之一。",en:"This hat will make you look like the Blue Power Larva, the famous masked justice fighter from Bonta."};
descriptions["14972"]={cn:"让你看起来像绿色战士，恐虫战队的成员之一。",en:"This hat will make you look like the Green Power Larva, the famous masked justice fighter from Bonta."};
descriptions["14974"]={cn:"是的，你没看错。唯一帮你提起裤子的东西，就是从腰带里渗出的粘稠液体。",en:"No, you\'re not going mad. The only thing holding your trousers up is, indeed, this viscous and sticky liquid dripping from your belt."};
descriptions["14976"]={cn:"是的，你没看错。唯一帮你提起裤子的东西，就是从腰带里渗出的粘稠液体。",en:"No, you\'re not going mad. The only thing holding your trousers up is, indeed, this viscous and sticky liquid dripping from your belt."};
descriptions["14978"]={cn:"黏糊糊的护肩，让人恶心。就算是你老妈也不愿意拥抱你。",en:"These epaulettes are so slimy and disgusting that even your own mother won\'t want to give you a hug."};
descriptions["14980"]={cn:"黏糊糊的护肩，让人恶心。就算是你老妈也不愿意拥抱你。",en:"These epaulettes are so slimy and disgusting that even your own mother won\'t want to give you a hug."};
descriptions["14982"]={cn:"谁能想到这世界上有这么大的变异虫？",en:"Who would have thought a Larva could be so big?"};
descriptions["14984"]={cn:"谁能想到这世界上有这么大的变异虫？",en:"Who would have thought a Larva could be so big?"};
descriptions["14986"]={cn:"想知道这里面藏着哪只豆芙远征队的人偶吗？",en:"Who knows which figurine from the  Brotherhood of the Tofu you might find hiding in this incredible Trinket Box?"};
descriptions["14987"]={cn:"想知道这里面藏着哪只酷洛大师第一季人偶吗？",en:"Who knows which Krosmaster season one figurine you might find hiding in this incredible Trinket Box?"};
descriptions["14989"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["14991"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["14993"]={cn:"如果护符坏了，那是因为乌鸦整天在树皮上又啄又扯的缘故。",en:"If this amulet is in bad condition, blame the Crobaks that spend their days pecking and tearing at Treechnids\' bark."};
descriptions["14994"]={cn:"使用远古树精天然树脂拼接而成。虽然经常会黏住一些小虫子，但是质地坚韧。",en:"This cape was put together using the Ancestral Treechnid\'s natural sap. It\'s always getting fluff stuck in its cracks, but at least it\'s solid."};
descriptions["14995"]={cn:"但愿远古树精的树皮比它的牙齿坚硬。",en:"Let\'s hope the Ancestral Treechnid\'s bark is stronger than his bite."};
descriptions["14996"]={cn:"戒指不错...从客观角度来讲。你戴起来漂亮极了。我可不想要，可是你戴确实不错...",en:"This ring is nice... I mean, in an understated way. It looks good on you. I wouldn\'t wear one myself, but you know..."};
descriptions["14997"]={cn:"大多数靴子刚穿起来的时候都有点硌脚，但是穿这双靴子却像在脚上插了一根荆棘刺！看来你必须忍受折磨才能成为真英雄。",en:"Most boots hurt a bit until they\'re worn in, but these ones will be a thorn in your side all the time! Sometimes you just have to suffer to be a hero."};
descriptions["14998"]={cn:"大象莱尼要发疯了...！她刚把那堆树干包裹妥当，而你却把它戴在了头上！",en:"Lenny the Elephant is going to be so mad...! She\'d only just packed that trunk and now you\'ve got it on your head!"};
descriptions["15001"]={cn:"除了它们该去的地方以外，其他地方都去过。",en:"These boots have been absolutely everywhere... except the place they were meant to go."};
descriptions["15002"]={cn:"穿上这双靴子，你会变得和著名的邦塔执政官一样活泼有干劲。",en:"Whap these boots on and you\'ll be as alive and kicking as the renowned Bontarian Governor."};
descriptions["15003"]={cn:"萨迪达的所有孩子都知道欧吉的故事，一个曾经尝试跟踪萨迪达神的人，他只希望变得更强。",en:"All Sadida children know the story of Orky, a Sadida who tried to track down the god Sadida to become more powerful."};
descriptions["15004"]={cn:"靴子曾经的主人一个时间法师曾试图通过倒着走来...使时间倒流。",en:"The bright spark of a Xelor who used to own these boots tried to turn back time... by walking backwards."};
descriptions["15005"]={cn:"曾经属于一位宝藏猎人。他始终戴着它。掩盖自己身份的同时，也遮住自己的真面目。有传言说他看上去像个巨魔。",en:"This mask belonged to an Enutrof. He wore it constantly, not so much to protect his identity as to veil his face; it\'s said he looked like a Trool."};
descriptions["15006"]={cn:"这件头盔属于一位勤勉的蒸汽行者档案管理员，他倾尽全部的退休生活致力于编著十二世界的历史和传说。",en:"This helmet belonged to an industrious Foggernaut archivist who dedicated the whole of his obsolescence to chronicling the history and lore of the World of Twelve."};
descriptions["15007"]={cn:"曾属于一位萨弗基亚执政官，他喜欢花好几个小时盯着镜子欣赏他的头冠。他被自己吓到了。",en:"This visor once belonged to a Sufokian governor, who started wearing it after developing a nasty habit of admiring his crown in the looking glass for hours at a time. He was starting to be dazzled by his own glory."};
descriptions["15008"]={cn:"属于一个卑劣的阴谋家，他的真实身份仍然是个迷。",en:"This skull belongs to a lowly con artist whose real identity is shrouded in mystery. Perhaps a certain Sugalo could shed some light on it?"};
descriptions["15009"]={cn:"有效抵挡任何侵略。",en:"Vewy pwacticaw pwotection against aw kinds of aggwessions."};
descriptions["15010"]={cn:"你也许见过不会笑的喵喵，但是你见过不会喵喵的笑吗？",en:"You\'ve probably seen a Bow Meow without a smile, but have you ever seen a smile without a Bow Meow?"};
descriptions["15011"]={cn:"曾经属于一位狡猾的弓手，莉莉斯。她试图尝试让人们相信她是个魔族，但是她只会在战斗中扔扔石头。",en:"These epaulettes belonged to a wily Cra known as Lilyx. She tried to make people believe she was a Shushu, but all she did during battles was throw stones."};
descriptions["15012"]={cn:"制造这对护肩需要大量艾卡利花粉，这种花粉来自于稀有的艾卡菲利花。",en:"The production of these epaulettes calls for a large quantity of pollen from the rare and beautiful Ecalipse flower."};
descriptions["15013"]={cn:"现如今卡玛很管用。",en:"The kama is strong these days. Hit \'em where it hurts, right in the shares!"};
descriptions["15015"]={cn:"一股热带季风迎面吹来，带来清新的海风气味。",en:"This ring brings the sea air rushing back with all the force of a tropical windstorm."};
descriptions["15016"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["15017"]={cn:"注意：戴上发着荧光的帽子并不意味着你变身幽灵，切勿模仿穿墙的把戏！",en:"Warning: just because you have a Ghostofied hat now doesn\'t mean you can walk through walls."};
descriptions["15019"]={cn:"前任主人不堪海盗骚扰，辞官隐退。海盗死后化为幽灵仍然纠缠着帽子的新主人！",en:"This hat\'s ex-wearer was infested with buccanits! They\'re still there, but in Ghostof form!"};
descriptions["15020"]={cn:"有点紧。老实说，如果你能够穿上一件幽灵缠绕的衣服，你显然不会因为外观这种细节问题而沮丧。",en:"This breastplate is a little too tight, but to be honest, if you\'re happy wearing a garment made of old Ghostofs, you obviously don\'t care much about your appearance."};
descriptions["15021"]={cn:"遇险的时候用生命保护你，太冷的时候温暖你，太热的时候为你扇风乘凉。还有比它更好的朋友吗？",en:"A breastplate that will not only protect you with its own life, but that will also cool you down when it\'s hot and keep you warm when it\'s cold!"};
descriptions["15022"]={cn:"如果一阵风吹过，披风会变成绿色并剧烈抖动。",en:"Just so you know, if you ever feel some trapped wind letting loose, this cloak will turn green and start vibrating violently."};
descriptions["15023"]={cn:"太紧了，让你不停喘气...",en:"A belt so tight that it might just make you want to heave..."};
descriptions["15024"]={cn:"没有人知道黑珍珠将军的真实身份，但是连腰带都以他命名，他本人一定酷毙了。",en:"Nobody knows who Admiral Hurl was, but to have a belt like this named after him, he must have been a pretty cool guy."};
descriptions["15025"]={cn:"内置的通风系统能24小时排汗。",en:"These epaulettes\' inbuilt ventilation system will have you churning out stale, piratey air 24/7."};
descriptions["15026"]={cn:"快来试试这对肩甲！看起来黑珍珠船长迫切想要锻炼他的肱二头肌。",en:"Get a load of the shoulder pads in these! Either the Captain of the Dark Hurl was living in the past, or he seriously needed to work on his muscles."};
descriptions["15027"]={cn:"在甲醛中浸泡多年，看上去不太可怕。但愿如此...",en:"This eye has been preserved in formaldehyde for decades so that it won\'t look too disgusting. It\'s the thought that counts..."};
descriptions["15028"]={cn:"这两块破布能盖住你的双肩。破布十分易燃，所以最好不要在西迪莫特火山附近行走。",en:"These rags will cover your shoulders. They\'re very flammable so you might want to avoid walking near the Sidimote volcano with them on."};
descriptions["15029"]={cn:"在黑珍珠号上发现的神秘披风。据说千年前曾属于一位著名的海盗。",en:"This mysterious cloak was found aboard the Dark Hurl. The rumor is that it once belonged to a famous Dofus-era pirate."};
descriptions["15030"]={cn:"打牌时出老千的优秀道具。",en:"This belt offers a handy spot for pirates to store their aces when playing cards (everyone knows their sleeves were long ago ripped off by raging captains, crocodiles, or the wear and tear of sea life)."};
descriptions["15031"]={cn:"海盗喜欢打牌来消磨时间。这套牌就是传说中的幸运套牌。里面包含了至少9张A。",en:"All the pirates idle much of their time away playing cards. This pack was THE lucky pack, which might have something to do with the fact that it contains no fewer than 9 aces."};
descriptions["15032"]={cn:"曾被用来消灭异种滋滋，维护夜晚的宁静。效果良好，可怜的异种滋滋现在已经绝迹了。",en:"This bow was once used to annihilate nocturnal invaders such as Exotic Moskitos. It was so efficient that the poor things are now extinct."};
descriptions["15033"]={cn:"曾经属于黑珍珠船长的佩剑。人不离剑，剑不离人...船长战死之后，他的佩剑也变成了幽灵。",en:"This sword used to belong to the Captain of the Dark Hurl. The two were inseparable... When the pirate captain died, his sword became a Ghostof too."};
descriptions["15034"]={cn:"当锤子敲击大地的时候，散发出一股令人作呕的气味。你最好学着远程战斗，而且要快！",en:"When this hammer hits the ground, a nauseating stench fills the vicinity. It\'s in your best interest to learn how to fight from a distance, and fast!"};
descriptions["15035"]={cn:"100%幽灵纤维制成。世代相传的好靴子！",en:"These boots are made of 100% authentic Ghostof fabric. They\'re gonna live forever!"};
descriptions["15036"]={cn:"如果戒指发出喘息声，不用紧张。因为有一个饱受折磨的海盗灵魂寄居其上。",en:"If your finger starts breathing by itself when you put this ring on, relax: it\'s just the soul of a tortured pirate who\'s been trapped inside for several decades."};
descriptions["15037"]={cn:"蕴含了高科技的盾牌，能从捕获的所有灵魂中吸取精华，转化为自身的防御力。硬度与粘度俱佳！",en:"This high-tech shield draws its resistance from all the souls it has captured. Its hardiness is matched only by its stickiness!"};
descriptions["15038"]={cn:"不是我夸你，但是你戴这顶帽子确实很帅。",en:"No need to toot your own horn, but you look very respecta-bull with this hat on."};
descriptions["15039"]={cn:"你说什么？你昨天刚见过？他们已经死了20多年了...！",en:"What do you mean, you saw them just yesterday? They\'ve been dead for twenty yeeeaaars...!"};
descriptions["15040"]={cn:"这把铲子有很多宝藏猎人拥趸，因为他们坚信铲子能为他们找到宝藏。实际上只能挖到没洗的短裤。信仰是盲目的。",en:"Many Enutrofs swear loyalty to this shovel because they think it will help them find treasure. All it ever seems to dig up is dirty underpants, though. Is faith really this blind?"};
descriptions["15041"]={cn:"哟呵呵呵，海盗哟，独眼哟，一只手是铁钩哟，哟呵呵呵...",en:"Ohhhhhhhh, a pirate\'s life is a life for you, with a hook hand here, and a yo-ho-ho..."};
descriptions["15042"]={cn:"总比二副好。",en:"At least it\'s better than Second Mate."};
descriptions["15043"]={cn:"锚去哪里了？吼一嗓子找水手长！",en:"Got you a hankerin\' for some anchorin\'? Caaaall the boatswain!"};
descriptions["15044"]={cn:"上膛！砰砰！",en:"Fire up the projectopult! All clear!"};
descriptions["15045"]={cn:"乘风逐浪！",en:"Hold the wave good and hold good the wind!"};
descriptions["15046"]={cn:"料理好船上那帮饿死鬼真是小菜一碟，就是吃了上顿没下顿而已...",en:"Serving the grub on a boat is easy as pie. It\'s keeping it down that\'s the hard part..."};
descriptions["15047"]={cn:"我的故事和你的故事一样，只是后面多了一章！\n- 海军准将，纳灵顿",en:"My story is exactly the same as your story, just one chapter behind!  Commodore Nubbington"};
descriptions["15048"]={cn:"向您报告，敬礼！",en:"Reporting for duty, SAH!"};
descriptions["15049"]={cn:"一般一般天下第三！",en:"You\'re halfway to half mast!"};
descriptions["15050"]={cn:"上膛！砰砰！",en:"Fire up the projectopult! All clear!"};
descriptions["15051"]={cn:"全员登船！",en:"Aaaall aboard!"};
descriptions["15052"]={cn:"料理好船上那帮饿死鬼真是小菜一碟，就是吃了上顿没下顿而已...",en:"Serving the grub on a boat is easy as pie. It\'s keeping it down that\'s the hard part..."};
descriptions["15053"]={cn:"像一个真正的邦塔人一样吹口哨！",en:"Whistle like a true Bontarian!"};
descriptions["15054"]={cn:"像一个真正的布拉克玛人一样吹口哨！",en:"Whistle like a true Brakmarian!"};
descriptions["15055"]={cn:"像一个真正的阿玛克纳人一样吹口哨！",en:"Whistle like a true Amaknian!"};
descriptions["15056"]={cn:"像一个真正的萨弗基亚人一样吹口哨！",en:"Whistle like a true Sufokian!"};
descriptions["15057"]={cn:"圣诞节来了，不要再犹豫，展现你内心的狂热，向敌人进攻！",en:"It\'s Kwismas, so bring out your inner Iop and charge at your enemies without a second\'s thought."};
descriptions["15058"]={cn:"啦啦啦吼！",en:"Laaaaand ho!"};
descriptions["15059"]={cn:"等等，大卫·琼斯的心脏在哪儿...？",en:"But where be Gravy Jones\'s heart...?"};
descriptions["15060"]={cn:"害羞是一种委婉说法，象征着机灵、油滑、狡猾以及绝对的邪恶！",en:"In this case, \'shy\' is a euphemism for shrewd, slippery, cunning, and downright devious!"};
descriptions["15061"]={cn:"在圣诞季里远离暴力，这就是你需要的。医治你的盟友...如果你愿意，甚至可以治愈你的敌人。",en:"If you abstain from violence during the Kwismas season, this is the costume for you. Heal your allies... and even your enemies, if you really want."};
descriptions["15062"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["15063"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["15064"]={cn:"在黑珍珠船长消失之前，他留给你了一个惊喜，就是这个袋子，在你满心欢喜要打开它的同时别忘记捂住你的鼻子...",en:"Before he disappeared, the Captain of the Dark Hurl left you a little surprise, and it\'s right here in this bag. Do yourself a favor and hold your nose whilst opening it..."};
descriptions["15066"]={cn:"礼物清单...圣诞老人的礼物清单！",en:"A wish list... Father Kwismas\'s wish list!"};
descriptions["15067"]={cn:"好像在嫌你显得不够蠢似的，现在朋友们都抢着坐到你的膝盖上拔你的胡子！",en:"As if you didn\'t feel stupid enough in this seasonal costume, now all your friends are trying to sit on your knee and play with your beard!"};
descriptions["15068"]={cn:"宠物染料可以于宠物设定介面中更改。此物品已无用处，可以将其分解掉。",en:"Pet colorings can be changed in the pet settings interface. This item is obsolete; you can recycle it."};
