descriptions["15088"]={cn:"放在你的圣诞树下。拾贰月25日之后可以打开。",en:"This pretty gift is yours to place under the Kwismas Tree of your choice. It can be opened from Descendre 25th onwards."};
descriptions["15089"]={cn:"这份文件授予你\"970年度十二世界最佳\"称号。蕾顿·麦克艾伦为你骄傲！",en:"This document enables you to claim the title of Miss or Mister World of Twelve 970. Yungold McFroggileg would be so proud of you!"};
descriptions["15090"]={cn:"前往地下城门口的兑奖机处兑换酷炫的奖励。",en:"Use the machine across from the dungeon to exchange your tokens for fantastic rewards."};
descriptions["15091"]={cn:"前往地下城门口的兑奖机处兑换酷炫的奖励。",en:"Use the machine across from the dungeon to exchange your tokens for fantastic rewards."};
descriptions["15092"]={cn:"在这片海洋，只有你说了算。",en:"A battle trophy to remind you of your victory in the dungeon."};
descriptions["15093"]={cn:"纪念你与那帮石头脑袋惊心动魄的战斗。",en:"A battle trophy to remind you of your victory in the dungeon."};
descriptions["15094"]={cn:"宠物装备可以于宠物设定介面中更改。此物品已无用处，可以将其分解掉。",en:"Pet equipment can be changed in the pet settings interface. This item is obsolete; you can recycle it."};
