descriptions["15097"]={cn:"宠物装备可以于宠物设定介面中更改。此物品已无用处，可以将其分解掉。",en:"Pet equipment can be changed in the pet settings interface. This item is obsolete; you can recycle it."};
descriptions["15098"]={cn:"在那山的这边海的那边有一群史努福，它们聪明又忠诚，干净又美丽...记得不要再它们面前泄露钱财...",en:"The Snoofle is clean-living, honest, and loyal. All the same, keep your Pouches out of sight when it\'s around."};
descriptions["15099"]={cn:"幸亏胡萝卜没有在奥古之乱中灭绝。要不没了那些活蹦乱跳的小生灵，这日子还怎么过呢？",en:"Thank goodness Ogrest\'s Chaos didn\'t destroy Cawwots. Where would you be without your bouncy little buddy?"};
descriptions["15100"]={cn:"只要在它面前摆上一堆排泄物，这只牛蝇就会变得十分听话。你甚至都不需要买宠物粮食。",en:"This Moofly is very affectionate, as long as you keep it next to things that have been digested at least once. Provide for it as you will."};
descriptions["15103"]={cn:"你已被吞噬。",en:"Cloak yourself in chaos."};
descriptions["15104"]={cn:"神奇的帽子，抖一抖，能召唤出没牙的巫婆、醉汉以及长角的胡萝卜到处跟着你。你真走运！",en:"This proud tricorn will have toothless hags, beery ruffians, and peg-legged parrots following you everywhere you go. You lucky thing!"};
descriptions["15105"]={cn:"混合了其他三个圣诞精灵的特点。给捣蛋鬼的完美礼物！好好珍惜，它很快就会消失的...",en:"This costume is a mixture of the three other Kwismas roles. The perfect gift for little mischief-makers! Make the most of it, as it won\'t last forever..."};
descriptions["15106"]={cn:"在海滩边上捡起一块漂亮的贝壳，在上面挖两个洞，大功告成。游客们最好骗了！",en:"Choose a pretty shell off the beach, drill two holes in it, and you\'ve got yourself a product. Tourists love this stuff!"};
descriptions["15111"]={cn:"真可惜，这件胸甲居然没有更大号的。否则你就可以整天呆在里面，把自己蜷成一团，一整天在海滩上吹风，无忧无虑。",en:"Too bad this breastplate isn\'t bigger, or else you could curl up inside it and chill on the beach all day, safe from harm."};
descriptions["15112"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["15113"]={cn:"足够吓跑任何尝试对你玩恶作剧的人。危险，高压！",en:"This cape should be enough to startle anyone trying to play a nasty trick on you. Danger, high voltage!"};
descriptions["15114"]={cn:"等等！你得知道一旦戴上就取不下来了。除非你想把所有的头发都扯下来。",en:"WAIT! Before you put this hat on, know that it\'s forever. Unless, of course, you\'re interested in ripping all your hair out trying to get it off."};
descriptions["15115"]={cn:"不要把戒指和炸爱鱿圈搞混了。你的牙齿会遭殃的。",en:"Make sure you don\'t mix this ring up with a Kralove donut. Your teeth will be sorely disappointed."};
descriptions["15116"]={cn:"软软的胸甲，一下子就黏上了皮肤。据说会造成65%的穿戴者的过敏反应！这就是为什么它只卖半价的原因...",en:"This gloopy breastplate sticks fast to your skin and is known to give 65% of wearers allergic reactions! So that\'s why it was half price..."};
descriptions["15117"]={cn:"别打死结。你可不想把刺激性的东西挂在你的腰间。",en:"Make sure you don\'t stick the two ends of this belt together. You don\'t want irritant bits near your... irritable bits."};
descriptions["15118"]={cn:"戴着这对护肩，你看起来像个有钱人。",en:"With these sailor-made epaulettes on your shoulders, you look very whelk-to-do indeed."};
descriptions["15119"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["15120"]={cn:"戴起来十分舒适。它还会时不时放几下电，让你时刻保持警惕。",en:"This helmet is comfortable enough on, but it has a tendency to let out a little electric shock from time to time, just to keep you on your toes."};
descriptions["15121"]={cn:"你见过这东西吗？它们在水里泡了很久！它们依然很没用，但是看起来不错，不是吗？",en:"Oh man, have you seen these things? They swell up in the water! I mean, that doesn\'t make them any more useful, but still! Cool, right?"};
descriptions["15122"]={cn:"工作狂！它已经擦干净了500只箭头、900个炸弹以及无数独角仙便便。",en:"This breastplate is a workaholic! It\'s already mopped up about 500 arrows, 900 bombs and countless Scaraleaf droppings."};
descriptions["15123"]={cn:"一码通用的腰带。菊芋片吃多了可以系起来防止肚子饱胀。",en:"A belt that really is one-size-fits-all. Pretty useful if you\'ve gone overboard on the Artichoke Chips!"};
descriptions["15124"]={cn:"会在战斗中爆炸...十万伏特！",en:"Epaulectrics explode into battle - lightning strikes!"};
descriptions["15125"]={cn:"吉他手丰古斯·杨的最爱。拉森努斯·华莱士从他那里偷得了这件披风，希望能从中吸取一些摇滚明星的精髓。",en:"This cloak was a firm favorite of guitarist Fungus Young\'s, before Larsenus Wallace stole it from him in the hopes of absorbing some of its rockstar essence."};
descriptions["15126"]={cn:"用于存放有关于十二神的所有书籍。",en:"Just what you needed to display your collection of books on the Twelve."};
descriptions["15127"]={cn:"如果你不知道这把弓的使用方法，你可以把它当成法杖来用。只有骑士才不知道怎么用这把弓。",en:"If you don\'t know how to use this bow, you can always pretend it\'s a staff. Then again, only a real Iop doesn\'t know how to use a bow."};
descriptions["15128"]={cn:"一旦你成功用这把锤子击败了敌人，那么千万不要再用第二次！里面的恶魔会苏醒过来，更加疯狂邪恶。",en:"If you manage to knock your target out with this hammer, whatever you do, don\'t hit it again! It might just come back to life, madder and badder than ever!"};
descriptions["15129"]={cn:"哦哦，快来看这只可爱的戒指，上面还有个小天线...噗呲呲呲！",en:"Awww, just look at this adorable little ring, with its little antennae and... BZZZT!"};
descriptions["15131"]={cn:"前往地下城门口的兑奖机处兑换酷炫的奖励。",en:"Use the machine across from the dungeon to exchange your tokens for fantastic rewards."};
descriptions["15132"]={cn:"从大王爱鱿身上移除之后，这只角就学乖了...然而，你得记住，永远不要相信睡眠中的蚌蚌。",en:"Once removed from the Kralaboss, this horn should behave itself... Still, as they say, never trust a sleeping Mollusky."};
descriptions["15133"]={cn:"腰带上系着这把钥匙，你可以轻易进入圣诞老人的小屋。也许你该去看看他是不是正忙着为世界各地的小朋友制作礼物。",en:"With this key on your belt, you can get into Father Kwismas\'s place without any hassle from the door-elves. Maybe you should go and make sure he\'s hard at work making gifts for the World\'s children."};
descriptions["15135"]={cn:"用于兑换圣诞节世界奖励，兑奖机就在圣诞老人旁边。",en:"Use this token to obtain Kwismas World rewards from the Machine just next to Father Kwismas."};
descriptions["15136"]={cn:"圣诞披风正式版！",en:"It\'s official! This is Father Kwismas\'s cloak!"};
descriptions["15137"]={cn:"圣诞帽！正式版！",en:"It\'s official! This is Father Kwismas\'s hat!"};
descriptions["15138"]={cn:"圣诞上衣！正式版！",en:"It\'s official! This is Father Kwismas\'s coat!"};
descriptions["15139"]={cn:"圣诞靴！正式版！",en:"It\'s official! These are Father Kwismas\'s boots!"};
descriptions["15140"]={cn:"嘿，我说，你得胆子够大才能穿！",en:"This \'ere costume is cursed! Be ye brave enough to wear it?"};
descriptions["15141"]={cn:"告诉朋友和爱人，你已经加入了黑暗帝国！",en:"Trick your friends and loved ones into thinking that you\'ve joined the dark side of the force with this insignia!"};
descriptions["15142"]={cn:"告诉朋友和爱人，你已经加入了黑暗帝国！",en:"Trick your friends and loved ones into thinking that you\'ve joined the dark side of the force with this insignia!"};
descriptions["15143"]={cn:"终于，你可以喘着粗气，睁着贼眼去散步了。",en:"Finally, an outfit to go with your heavy breathing and shifty eyes."};
descriptions["15144"]={cn:"多亏了这件装束，你再也不用为领导一堆狂热的蒙面人而烦恼了。",en:"Thanks to this great hat, you won\'t have any problem leading your ga... your guild of fervent Hoodlums."};
descriptions["15145"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["15146"]={cn:"见过碎石者表演一种古代摔跤技巧...头槌吗？你见到的时候，最好戴着这顶头盔。",en:"If you\'ve ever seen a Crackrock performing the ancient fight move known as a headbutt, you\'ll know that you\'re better off inside this helmet than out."};
descriptions["15147"]={cn:"不是个拿来跑100卡米的好选择。在千洞林藏身还不错。",en:"A bad cloak for running the 100 kameters in. A good cloak for blending into your surroundings in the Holey Forest!"};
descriptions["15148"]={cn:"自从绵球球大赛禁止穿寒石靴以后，到处都可以买到它们。显然不是什么高级货。",en:"These boots have been readily available ever since they were banned from Gobbowl tournaments. Apparently they weren\'t hardcore enough."};
descriptions["15149"]={cn:"如果你不是狂热战士，最好还是不要穿上这件胸甲。",en:"You could also use it as a Poutch Ingball, but I wouldn\'t recommend it unless you\'re a Sacrier."};
descriptions["15150"]={cn:"你知道吗，制作这枚戒指的石材是从新出生的婴儿手中抢来的。有时候，冷酷无情是最佳选择。",en:"Did you know the stones used to make this ring were wrestled off their owners the moment they were born? Sometimes, cruelty is the best option."};
descriptions["15151"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["15152"]={cn:"穿上披风，闪亮登场！",en:"Erupt onto the scene with this scalding hot cloak! Do you have any idea how hard it is to hold on to these things?"};
descriptions["15153"]={cn:"戴上它，你会觉得自己化身成为杀戮机器。简单来讲，你会发狂的。",en:"Put this ring on and you\'ll think you\'re the next mechanic destructive commando. In short, you\'ll blow your top."};
descriptions["15155"]={cn:"寒石胸甲的升级版。熔岩碎石者会抓住你的双手，你再怎么叫也不会有人来的。",en:"One step up from the Stone Cold Breastplate, the Magmacrak variety will not only bust your fists when you punch it, but also singe their hairs right to the skin!"};
descriptions["15156"]={cn:"不推荐在舞厅穿着。不仅会踩烂舞伴的脚，你会把她们烫死！",en:"These boots aren\'t recommended for the Clockwork Ball. You won\'t just step on your date\'s feet; you\'ll burn them right off!"};
descriptions["15157"]={cn:"与其让你自己的脖子受苦，不如让你的敌人吃点苦头。",en:"Rather than cricking your own neck, why not crick your adversaries\'?"};
descriptions["15158"]={cn:"完全不用担心衣着冷暖！",en:"With a Petra-Pack on your arm, your basic necessities won\'t move an inch!"};
descriptions["15159"]={cn:"看来有人经常写错别字...没有人会当着你的面提起这件事，尤其是当你脸色铁青的时候。",en:"Looks like someone came last in the spelling bee... All the same, nobody would ever say it to your face, not when you look this scary."};
descriptions["15160"]={cn:"男人只因浪漫铭记爱情。",en:"Once you get back from your adventures, you\'ve sworn to SOMEHOW add this piece to the epic marble run leading from your bedroom to the garage, passing through all the rooms in the house. But now, brave Ulysses, is not the time for play. It is the time for fighting; for fighting and glory!"};
descriptions["15161"]={cn:"能一口气把牙菌斑清扫干净。布拉克玛口腔卫生协会专业认证。",en:"This staff hits so hard it\'ll knock the plaque right off your enemy\'s teeth. Approved by the Brakmarian Dental Association."};
descriptions["15162"]={cn:"就算是皇家碎石者都免不了粘点胡子装样子！",en:"Even the Royal Crackler dons a little ginger goatee for Movamaire!"};
descriptions["15163"]={cn:"据说能为佩戴者带来神秘的强作微笑的力量。仔细看看，你就知道这股力量一点也不神秘了。",en:"This ring is said to confer a mystical smile-cracking power on its wearer. Looking at it, though, perhaps it\'s not so mystical after all."};
descriptions["15164"]={cn:"你忍不住想打自己的头，也包括敌人的头！",en:"The only breastplate that will make you want to bop your head - and your enemies\' heads!"};
descriptions["15165"]={cn:"记住：时刻倾听自己的内心！",en:"Just remember: always let your Conchus be your guide!"};
descriptions["15166"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["15167"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["15168"]={cn:"头盔上的白牙依旧十分锋利，所以要么脱下来，否则你得当心你的鼻子了！",en:"This hat\'s teeth are still very sharp, so file \'em down or watch your nose!"};
descriptions["15169"]={cn:"取自于那些恐水的鲨鱼，制造这对护肩的纤维防水性能极佳。",en:"Just like any self-respecting, aquaphobic Shark, the fabric used to make these epaulettes is 100% rainproof."};
descriptions["15170"]={cn:"在撒克雅女神的婚礼上，这枚戒指从此戴在了她的手上。很显然，这样的戒指她都收到过几十枚了，不过这份心意毕竟给到了。",en:"This is the ring the goddess Sacrier was offered for her hand in marriage. Obviously, she already had dozens like it, but it\'s the thought that counts."};
descriptions["15171"]={cn:"散发着起码五十种不同的血腥味。比如草莓味的治愈者鲜血以及木糖醇口味的植物术士鲜血，当然还有少许熊猫武僧的酒味鲜血。",en:"There must be at least fifty shades of blood on this cloak, from fruity Eniripsa blood to wood-scented Sadida blood, not forgetting a few healthy spatters of milky Pandawa blood."};
descriptions["15172"]={cn:"很锋利的腰带，不要怀疑，流下来的血是你的。快叫救护车！",en:"If that belt is anywhere near as sharp as it looks, some of the blood dripping off it is definitely yours. Call a medic!"};
descriptions["15173"]={cn:"仍然滴着鲜血。穆斯堂上校在锅炉房犯下鱼叉谋杀案的时候，就穿着这件披风。",en:"There\'s fresh blood still dripping from this cloak. Colonel Mustang was wearing it when he committed a murder in the boiler room with the harpoon. That game didn\'t last long."};
descriptions["15174"]={cn:"沾满血迹，阴森可怖。你从同伴的尸体上拾取了这对护肩，现在你只想把它们脱下来！",en:"You just want to take these they\'re Blood-Stained Epaulettes and you just want them off!"};
descriptions["15175"]={cn:"别妄想戴着这枚戒指去蒸汽海岸。如果被那里的生物闻到血腥味，它们才不管究竟是你还是你的戒指发出的。",en:"Don\'t even think about getting near the Steamulating Shore with this ring. If they smell fresh blood, they won\'t care whether it\'s yours or your ring\'s."};
descriptions["15176"]={cn:"你腿上怎么有条纹？哦...对不起...仅仅是你的血而已。没事没事，我什么都没看到。",en:"Are those pin-striped legs you\'ve got there? Oh... Sorry... It\'s just the blood from your belt. That\'s embarrassing."};
descriptions["15177"]={cn:"布拉克玛最受欢迎的运动曾经是鲨鱼球。运动员们拼命地用鲨鱼斧击打一个骷髅。自从绵球球运动风靡之后，就再也没有人玩鲨鱼球了。",en:"Brakmar\'s favorite sport used to be Shaxball, in which competitors whacked at a Chafer Skull with a Shax. Ever since Gobbowl made it big, Shaxball has been largely forgotten."};
descriptions["15178"]={cn:"隐匿身形，发出可怕的声音，侦测树后的昆虫和蜘蛛...",en:"These boots are the bees\' knees at detecting insects and Arachnees hiding amongst the trees... being invisible... and making creepy clicking noises. Brrr!"};
descriptions["15179"]={cn:"仍然滴着受难者的鲜血。",en:"The messiest cards ever. Period."};
descriptions["15180"]={cn:"多亏了里面厚实的海藻，没有一颗子弹能穿透它。",en:"Thanksh to all the sheaweed inshide thish shield, not a shingle bullet will shucsheed in reaching you."};
descriptions["15181"]={cn:"你也许不知道鲨鱼也有肌肉，现在你知道了。觉得怎么样？它们可是世界上最坚硬的胸肌！",en:"You may not have known that they had pecs, but now that you do know, do you not agree that they must be among the toughest in the World?"};
descriptions["15182"]={cn:"袜子鼓鼓的，显然是有什么东西在里面！到底是什么？",en:"There\'s something rocking in your stocking! What is it?"};
descriptions["15183"]={cn:"可爱的名字，配上可怕的肩甲。啊呜！",en:"A cutesy-wutesy name for a pair of cutesy-wutesy... enormous... intimidating epaulettes. Gulp!"};
descriptions["15187"]={cn:"你觉得这会让你成为海滩派对的万人迷。事与愿违，你把所有人都吓跑了，派对也泡汤了。",en:"You thought this would be a great way to become \'the funny guy\' at beach parties; all it really does is turn off light switches when you\'re least expecting it."};
descriptions["15188"]={cn:"此卷轴能重置你所有的属性页面。\n打开属性页面列表以使用此卷轴，必须在此帐号内有等级至少 51 的角色才能解锁页面。\n此卷轴与帐号绑定，并会在使用后消耗掉。",en:"This scroll lets you reset ALL your Characteristics pages.\nTo use it, go to the list of Characteristics pages. You must have a character of level 51 or higher on your account to unlock this interface.\nThis scroll is linked to the account and will be consumed upon use."};
descriptions["15192"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["15193"]={cn:"由黑寡妇亲自一针一线、辛辛苦苦地缝制完成。投石机也对它无可奈何。还等什么，赶快穿上吧。",en:"This cloak was woven thread by thread by the meticulous Black Widow herself. A Catapulted Crackler would have no chance against it, so I don\'t know why you\'re so quick to put it on your back."};
descriptions["15194"]={cn:"黑寡妇有一大堆这种靴子。碰巧盗贼时尚杂志推荐它们为本季流行款！",en:"The Black Widow has tons of these boots to spare, which is just as well, because Rogue magazine says they\'re in this season!"};
descriptions["15195"]={cn:"依然保留着黑寡妇的致命毒液。最好不要送给喜欢在思考问题时咬项链的朋友。",en:"This amulet still contains some of the Black Widow\'s lethal venom. Best not offer it to that friend of yours who chews on her necklace when she\'s thinking hard."};
descriptions["15196"]={cn:"估计她再也不需要这玩意儿了，现在她可是个寡妇。",en:"I suppose she doesn\'t need it any more, now she\'s a widow."};
descriptions["15197"]={cn:"好像有一只超大的虱子在你的头发里钻来钻去。是不是觉得头皮发麻，双脚发软？",en:"This hair clasp makes you feel like a giant louse is wriggling around in your hair. Doesn\'t it give you the shivers?"};
descriptions["15198"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["15199"]={cn:"就算站在放射性的烂泥里也不会吓到你。当然，你还是会死...",en:"Standing in radioactive puddles won\'t faze you if you\'re wearing these shoes. I mean, you\'ll be doomed anyway, but you know..."};
descriptions["15200"]={cn:"看起来像南瓜节糖果，可是无法食用。",en:"This amulet may look like an Al Howin\'s Treat, but that\'s no reason to eat it."};
descriptions["15201"]={cn:"选择这枚戒指是个赌博：要么被咬掉手指头，要么你的手指长成原来的3倍。请三思而后行。",en:"This ring has a double-or-nothing thing going on: either it bites off your finger, or it makes your finger grow to three times its size. Think very carefully about the consequences before you put it on."};
descriptions["15202"]={cn:"你看上去像个发着荧光的伞菇！",en:"From above, you look like a radioactive toadstool!"};
descriptions["15203"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["15204"]={cn:"如果你的背上不能有一双额外的眼睛，至少你可以把它们戴在头上。",en:"If you can\'t have an extra set of eyes on your back, you can at least have them on your head."};
descriptions["15205"]={cn:"标签上写着“即使有摩擦也依然柔顺。”\n不幸的是，冒险者通常没有这特征。",en:"The label reads \"Gentle, even when rubbed the wrong way.\"\nA characteristic you often don\'t find with adventurers, unfortunately."};
descriptions["15206"]={cn:"闪闪发亮的腰带。在黑夜中行走时，让你的龙鸟清晰可见。",en:"This belt can also be used as a hi-vis band to make your Dragoturkey visible to other path users on dark nights."};
descriptions["15207"]={cn:"里里外外毛毛茸茸的。",en:"Hairy inside and out."};
descriptions["15208"]={cn:"眼睛比肚子还大。",en:"Your eyes are bigger than your belly."};
descriptions["15209"]={cn:"如果你已经戴上它，强烈建议你取下来。我们已经警告过你了...",en:"Once you\'ve put this ring on, it\'s highly recommended that you take it off again. You have been warned..."};
descriptions["15210"]={cn:"想拿起法杖仔细端详的蠢货最终都会受辐射变成三眼怪物。谨慎选择你的目标。",en:"Whatever numbskull takes this cudgel in the face is likely to sprout a third eye on a stalk. Choose your targets well."};
descriptions["15211"]={cn:"Alpha = beta * e (-Ln2 * t / T)\n看得懂吗？放心，没人看得懂！",en:"Alpha = Beta * e (-Ln2 * t / T)\nDon\'t understand? Neither does anyone else!"};
descriptions["15212"]={cn:"挥舞时闪烁着七彩的火花。也许对于环境并不好，但是漂亮极了！",en:"When used, this wand releases pretty sparks in all different colors. It\'s not very good for the planet, but it\'s so cute!"};
descriptions["15213"]={cn:"如果你发现身体发生了异变，别害怕...",en:"If you feel like your silhouette is no longer \"you\" when you\'re wearing these epaulettes, you\'re probably quite right. Don\'t be afraid..."};
descriptions["15214"]={cn:"带有黑寡妇的独特标记，引领你成为虫族的一员。嗯，其实蜘蛛不是昆虫...",en:"This cape, which bears the inimitable mark of the Black Widow, will probably get you free entry to a sect one of these days. An in-sect, that is!"};
descriptions["15215"]={cn:"黑寡妇诱惑了一只盘丝蜘蛛，然后掰下了它的一条腿来制造她的设计品，行为十分卑劣。",en:"The Black Widow bamboozled an Arachnee Embroiderer and nabbed one of its hands for her own dastardly designs."};
descriptions["15216"]={cn:"这件胸甲能为你带来钢铁般的胸肌。是的，我说的是钢铁般的胸肌。",en:"This breastplate will give you pecs of toxic steel. What? Pecs of steel. That\'s what I said."};
descriptions["15217"]={cn:"不用预先想好要挖掘的地点。它会自己找！",en:"Don\'t tell this shovel where to dig! It\'s not a serial number, it\'s a free spade!"};
descriptions["15218"]={cn:"你不是有健全的双腿么？站起来，向前走！",en:"Boots with a built-in rhythm system to make sure you step to the beat! That part in the pantomime might be yours at last!"};
descriptions["15219"]={cn:"点击两下来把整组古代资源转换成新的资源。古代资源需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["15220"]={cn:"用它来迎接你的敌人是再好不过的了，当你亲爱的姑母突然来访时，它也会成为你宝贵的盟友。",en:"The perfect thing to greet your enemies with, this venom will also be a valuable ally in the event of a surprise visit from your dear great aunt."};
descriptions["15221"]={cn:"他们说蜘蛛腿能带来好运。如果不奏效，你也可以把它吃了。经过油炸后，它们就成了美味的开胃菜！",en:"They say Arachnee legs bring good luck. If that doesn\'t work, you can always eat them. Deep-fried, they make a scrumptious appetizer!"};
descriptions["15222"]={cn:"被用来制造魔法道具，用完后随你怎么摆弄。",en:"This Rump is normally used to create magical objects, but once you\'re done with that, use it for whatever you like."};
descriptions["15223"]={cn:"前往地下城门口的兑奖机处兑换酷炫的奖励。",en:"Use the machine across from the dungeon to exchange your tokens for fantastic rewards."};
descriptions["15225"]={cn:"前往地下城门口的兑奖机处兑换酷炫的奖励。",en:"Use the machine across from the dungeon to exchange your tokens for fantastic rewards."};
descriptions["15226"]={cn:"你才是真正的老大。",en:"A battle trophy to remind you of your victory in the dungeon."};
descriptions["15227"]={cn:"天冷时鼓动蒸汽，暖意流遍全身。天热时流通护甲中的空气，凉爽舒适。",en:"This smart cookie of an amulet steams gently when it\'s cold outside and ventilates your armor during the summer."};
descriptions["15228"]={cn:"用力敲阿玛克纳钹，发出噪音。",en:"Try out the hi-hat, and instrument as cool as Amakna!"};
descriptions["15229"]={cn:"为什么护符会这么红？那是设计师一边看非诚勿扰一边不小心把指甲油涂上去的缘故。",en:"This amulet\'s disturbing red color is the result of many layers of nail varnish, idly applied whilst watching Kilmour Girls. At least, that\'s what the Sacrier who made it told the Kros Scene Investigation crew."};
descriptions["15230"]={cn:"最初这条护符的形状是个脑袋，但是试用的骑士坚持认为那是个水龙头...",en:"The initial design for this amulet was embossed with the shape of a brain, but the Iop test subjects kept thinking it was a bubblegum holder."};
descriptions["15231"]={cn:"用力吹阿玛克纳大号，发出噪音。",en:"Try out the tuba, a classic instrument from Amakna!"};
descriptions["15232"]={cn:"据说带有导航装置，能帮弓手自动瞄准。看来你的这条需要换电池了。",en:"This amulet is rumored to have a homing device installed to help you aim better. Yours might just need new batteries."};
descriptions["15233"]={cn:"脖子上挂着这枚护符，幸运猫无所不能。",en:"With a talisman like this round his neck, any Ecaflip would feel lucky."};
descriptions["15234"]={cn:"用力拉阿玛克纳低音提琴，发出噪音。",en:"Try out the double bass, a pleasing peasant instrument from Amakna!"};
descriptions["15235"]={cn:"始终保护着队友们。作为治愈者有时候也想自私一点。",en:"An amulet that will watch over its wearer\'s allies. Eniripsas must get bored of being so selfless."};
descriptions["15236"]={cn:"戴起来无比的轻松舒适，植物术士的最爱。",en:"This amulet is favored by Sadidas for its relaxing properties. Pfft - as if they need to be any more relaxed!"};
descriptions["15237"]={cn:"用力打邦塔小军鼓，发出噪音。",en:"Try out the snare drum, an instrument with a sound as bright as Bonta!"};
descriptions["15238"]={cn:"哦，你选择带头巾了。或许你太丑，不想以真面目示人...又或许你对于时尚流行的把握高人一等。",en:"Wearing a hood now, are you? Either you\'ve got something to hide... or you really are streets ahead when it comes to fashion."};
descriptions["15239"]={cn:"用力打邦塔低音鼓，发出噪音。",en:"Try out the bass drum, an emblematic Bontarian instrument!"};
descriptions["15240"]={cn:"某个大型冻结时间装置的一部分。当然，它一点用都没有。所以现在它只是个免费赠品。",en:"This amulet was part of a large-scale effort to freeze time. It didn\'t work, of course, so now they\'re giving away the amulets as promotional freebies."};
descriptions["15241"]={cn:"用力吹邦塔圆号，发出噪音。",en:"Try out the horn, an instrument of salvation straight from Bonta!"};
descriptions["15242"]={cn:"前任主人还以为永远失去了它。实际上只是被地穴兽吞了下去，这意味着...是的，它完好无损。",en:"The Enutrof this amulet used to belong to thought it had been lost forever. It had actually just been swallowed by his Drheller, which means... Yep. Still, all\'s well that ends well!"};
descriptions["15243"]={cn:"和它的主人一样诡计多端：如果它一旦失窃，会悄悄地从罪犯的指间溜走。",en:"This loyal amulet is as roguish as its master: if ever it gets stolen, it will slip and slide until it slithers out from between the criminal\'s fingers."};
descriptions["15244"]={cn:"能让所有者屹立不倒，即便是痛饮了10杯熊猫佳酿。",en:"This amulet\'s specialty is keeping its owner upright, even after ten tankards of Bamboo Milk."};
descriptions["15245"]={cn:"保护欲过强，有些时候，仅仅是有些时候，这并不是一件坏事。",en:"This amulet can be over-protective, but sometimes, just sometimes, that\'s not such a bad thing."};
descriptions["15246"]={cn:"只要野兽们看到你脖子上的护符，它们就会乖乖就范。",en:"When they spot this amulet dangling from your neck, your furry friends will know who\'s boss."};
descriptions["15247"]={cn:"用力弹布拉克玛贝司，发出噪音。",en:"Try out the bass, an instrument as deep as Brakmar!"};
descriptions["15248"]={cn:"保护你躲过各种窥视的目光。当然，前提是你背对着人群。",en:"This cloak will keep you hidden from prying eyes. Well, as long as you keep your back to people."};
descriptions["15249"]={cn:"用力打布拉克玛鼓，发出噪音。",en:"Try out the drums, an instrument as thunderous as Brakmar!"};
descriptions["15250"]={cn:"恭喜，聪明人！这双靴子用来追踪蒙面人集团是最好的。",en:"Congratulations, wise guy! These boots are the best in the World for tracking down the Hoodlum clan."};
descriptions["15251"]={cn:"用力弹布拉克玛电吉他，发出噪音。",en:"Try out the electric guitar, an instrument as chaotic and powerful as Brakmar!"};
descriptions["15252"]={cn:"用来破坏蒙面人会议十分有效。",en:"This ring will come in very useful when breaking up Hoodlum meetings."};
descriptions["15253"]={cn:"用力弹萨弗基亚四弦琴，发出噪音！",en:"Try out the ukulele, and experience the exotic markets of Sufokia!"};
descriptions["15254"]={cn:"用力吹萨弗基亚陶笛，发出噪音。",en:"Try out the ocarina, an instrument as mysterious as Sufokia!"};
descriptions["15255"]={cn:"让你潜伏于阴影之中，不被敌人发现。",en:"This amulet will ensure that you stay overshadowed by your opponents."};
descriptions["15256"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["15257"]={cn:"独特的徽章，戴起来之后化身骑士。",en:"This emblem carries an exclusive outfit that would look the business on your Iop."};
descriptions["15258"]={cn:"独特的徽章，戴起来之后化身弓手。",en:"This emblem carries an exclusive outfit that would look the business on your Cra."};
descriptions["15259"]={cn:"用力弹萨弗基亚木琴，发出噪音！",en:"Try out the vibes, and be cool, as cool as the Sufokian beaches!"};
descriptions["15260"]={cn:"独特的徽章，戴起来之后化身狂战士。",en:"This emblem carries an exclusive outfit that would look the business on your Sacrier."};
descriptions["15261"]={cn:"独特的徽章，戴起来之后化身幸运猫。",en:"This emblem carries an exclusive outfit that would look the business on your Ecaflip."};
descriptions["15262"]={cn:"独特的徽章，戴起来之后化身治愈者。",en:"This emblem carries an exclusive outfit that would look the business on your Eniripsa."};
descriptions["15263"]={cn:"独特的徽章，戴起来之后化身植物术士。",en:"This emblem carries an exclusive outfit that would look the business on your Sadida."};
descriptions["15264"]={cn:"独特的徽章，戴起来之后化身时间法师。",en:"This emblem carries an exclusive outfit that would look the business on your Xelor."};
descriptions["15265"]={cn:"独特的徽章，戴起来之后化身宝藏猎人。",en:"This emblem carries an exclusive outfit that would look the business on your Enutrof."};
descriptions["15266"]={cn:"独特的徽章，戴起来之后化身盗贼。",en:"This emblem carries an exclusive outfit that would look the business on your Rogue."};
descriptions["15267"]={cn:"独特的徽章，戴起来之后化身熊猫武僧。",en:"This emblem carries an exclusive outfit that would look the business on your Pandawa."};
descriptions["15268"]={cn:"独特的徽章，戴起来之后化身守护者。",en:"This emblem carries an exclusive outfit that would look the business on your Feca."};
descriptions["15269"]={cn:"独特的徽章，戴起来之后化身唤兽师。",en:"This emblem carries an exclusive outfit that would look the business on your Osamodas."};
descriptions["15270"]={cn:"独特的徽章，戴起来之后化身蒸汽行者。",en:"This emblem carries an exclusive outfit that would look the business on your Foggernaut."};
descriptions["15271"]={cn:"独特的徽章，戴起来之后化身刺客。",en:"This emblem carries an exclusive outfit that would look the business on your Sram."};
descriptions["15272"]={cn:"两个苹朵和这把弓，这是第一堂训练课上发的课件，省着点用，没多的...不满意？去教育局投诉吧。",en:"This bow comes with two double-A Apis for your first training session. Once you\'ve used them up, you\'ll have to buy your own fruit. Pfft... Consumerism, grmbl..."};
descriptions["15273"]={cn:"魔剑嗜血！浴血成魔！",en:"This sword feeds on the blood of its victims. The more blood it sheds, the more legendary it will become!"};
descriptions["15274"]={cn:"曾经属于一个叫做佩西莫尔的英雄。他究竟是怎样举起是他体重50倍的锤子的？没有人知道。",en:"This hammer used to belong to a Puddly named Percimol. How he carried a hammer 50 times his weight, we\'ll probably never know."};
descriptions["15275"]={cn:"不仅仅是治愈者，所有喜欢治疗队友的冒险者都可以使用。",en:"This wand isn\'t just for Eniripsas, but for all adventurers who like being hot on their heals."};
descriptions["15276"]={cn:"与恶臭得令人作呕的腐尸法杖不同，这柄法杖总是散发着一股诱人的陈年老木的香气。",en:"This staff has a pleasant, woody smell about it... not like that nasty Corpse Club, which stinks so bad no one can bear to be in the same room as it."};
descriptions["15277"]={cn:"这套卡牌以【A】多而闻名于世，总共有32张【A】。为什么说和幸运猫打牌到最后往往变成了吵架，你现在明白了吧。",en:"These cards are legendary for their disproportionately high number of aces. There are 32 in all. It goes without saying that most Ecaflip card games end in brawls."};
descriptions["15278"]={cn:"坏蛋？对，就是坏蛋！坏蛋阿乓！",en:"Big boom? Yeah, big boom! Big Bad Aboum boom!"};
descriptions["15279"]={cn:"拽住了别慌神，不然削掉自己几节手指头都不知道。",en:"Careful who you give this sword to. If you\'re the fragile sort, you might lose a fingertip or ten without realizing."};
descriptions["15280"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["15281"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["15282"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["15283"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["15284"]={cn:"你怒不可遏地想用头撞扁所有人。",en:"Whoever wears this helmet will feel an insatiable urge to headbutt the target."};
descriptions["15285"]={cn:"戴着这顶头盔，你可以肆无忌惮地横冲直撞。",en:"With this helmet on, you won\'t be afraid to plunge headlong into the fray to take hits on your allies\' behalf."};
descriptions["15286"]={cn:"头盔里藏着一只魔法兔兔。它并不会让观众捧腹大笑，只会让敌人嚎啕大哭。",en:"There\'s a Wodent hidden in this helmet, magician style. This one\'s not there to impress the crowd, but to squeak battle cries as you attack."};
descriptions["15287"]={cn:"专门设计的空气动力学套件，让你迅捷无比。酷洛运动会上见！",en:"This helmet has a specially designed aerodynamic cut to help you go faster. See you at the Krozolympiks!"};
descriptions["15288"]={cn:"这件胸甲曾经属于一个巨大的绿色的家伙，忘了叫什么来着。他变身成这么大只的怪物，身上的盔甲居然没有被撑破，还叫我们不要在意细节。",en:"This breastplate used to belong to some huge, green guy whose name has slipped my mind. Even when he transformed into an all-powerful monster, this armor remained intact."};
descriptions["15289"]={cn:"这件胸甲的防御能力有目共睹，你一穿上它就忍不住冲进敌人的密集火力区域，还一边像吃错了药一样大笑着。",en:"This breastplate\'s resistance is something to behold. The only thing you won\'t be able to resist is the urge to show it off by striding into a barrage of enemy fire, laughing like a madman."};
descriptions["15290"]={cn:"这件盔甲上安装了好几个小机关，用来暗中发射陷阱和炸弹。高科技真是猜不透啊！",en:"This armor is fitted with a row of little switches, so you can set off your traps or bombs on the go. Technology never ceases to amaze!"};
descriptions["15291"]={cn:"这位朋友，请问你的腿上是不是长了飞毛？要不然你怎么能这么快！",en:"Hey baby, is your name Bad News? Cos they say Bad News travels fast."};
descriptions["15292"]={cn:"能让善于背刺偷袭的战士们激动得无法坐下。",en:"This cloak was created to destabilize warriors whose forte was stabs in the back."};
descriptions["15293"]={cn:"曾属于你死去的保姆。好好用它。",en:"This cloak belonged to your nanny before she died. Use it well."};
descriptions["15294"]={cn:"闻到了吗?这是烤咕哩的香味。能保证你的召唤物始终知道你的位置。",en:"Can you smell that? That\'s the light fragrance of grilled Blibli. It\'ll ensure that your summons know exactly where you are at all times."};
descriptions["15295"]={cn:"穿着它切忌跑得太快，轻轻一跳就可以像马里奥一样撞到墙壁。",en:"Careful you don\'t run TOO fast with this cloak; the slightest jump will send you soaring into the air like a plumber!"};
descriptions["15296"]={cn:"穿着这对护肩，你就别再想笑了。",en:"With these epaulettes on, your laughing stock days are well and truly over."};
descriptions["15297"]={cn:"充满了到处搜罗来的乱七八糟的材料。穿起来十分不舒服，而且还和碎石者的头一样硬！",en:"These epaulettes have been stuffed with various materials found all around! They\'re hellishly uncomfortable but also harder than a Crackler\'s skull."};
descriptions["15298"]={cn:"最早的版本是由羊毛和猪皮制成的。但是自从植物术士的宝宝开始以环境保护的名义惩罚穿皮草制品的人之后，所有款式的原料都变了。",en:"The initial design for these epaulettes was in Gobball Wool and Blibli Leather, but all that changed when militant Sadida dolls started ambushing wearers in the name of environmental protection."};
descriptions["15299"]={cn:"迅疾如风，让你眨眼之间追上敌人。",en:"These epaulettes catch the wind and use it to propel you towards your enemies in the blink of an eye."};
descriptions["15300"]={cn:"你不怕雪！雪怕你！看见你过来雪都自己吹飞了！",en:"You ain\'t afraid of no snow! When it sees you comin\', it plows itself!"};
descriptions["15301"]={cn:"十二世界的好东西都想到你袋子里来，你就不能换个大点的袋子么？别伤心了。",en:"Your sack has enough gifts in it to satisfy the grabbing hands of the entire World of Twelve, so why so sad?"};
descriptions["15302"]={cn:"有的大炮用来传送人，有的大炮只能用来传送雪球。两者皆不可抛，切记。",en:"Some cannons transport people, and some cannons only transport snow, but they\'re both very important. Remember that."};
descriptions["15303"]={cn:"不仅是跳舞，已成为习俗！",en:"This is more than just a dance. This is a ritual!"};
descriptions["15304"]={cn:"100枚硬币，因爱铸就。",en:"100 little kamas, minted with love."};
descriptions["15305"]={cn:"6,000枚硬币，因爱铸就。",en:"6,000 little kamas, minted with love."};
descriptions["15306"]={cn:"300 枚硬币，因爱铸就。",en:"300 little kamas, minted with love."};
descriptions["15307"]={cn:"400枚硬币，因爱铸就。",en:"400 little kamas, minted with love."};
descriptions["15308"]={cn:"500枚硬币，因爱铸就。",en:"500 little kamas, minted with love."};
descriptions["15309"]={cn:"你当然有资格可以照看孩子！",en:"Qualified to take care of children? Of course you are!"};
descriptions["15311"]={cn:"这个袋子的容量之大足够你装下所有你喜欢的人偶，多少都可以！",en:"This bag is roomy enough to hold all your favorite figurines and much, much more!"};
descriptions["15315"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["15316"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["15317"]={cn:"让你一整天看起来潇洒倜傥...像个旋鸟一样翩翩起舞吧！",en:"These epaulettes will keep you cool all day long - and let you play at being a helicopter! Wheee!"};
descriptions["15318"]={cn:"皇家的旋转舞才够劲！",en:"When the whirl is not enough... try going Royal."};
descriptions["15319"]={cn:"在乌贼岛上很受欢迎，那里四季炎热如夏。在日光浴爱好者面前走过，他们会永生难忘。",en:"This cloak is most welcome on places like Calamar Island, where the heat is unbearable for much of the year. Twirl gently near the sunbathers and they\'ll be eternally grateful."};
descriptions["15320"]={cn:"显然，这枚戒指的拥有者将可以从树上优雅地转到地上。它曾经属于一个刺客，但是戒指的力量让他疯狂了。",en:"Apparently, anyone who puts this ring on will have the magical power to twirl gracefully down from a tree to the ground. It used to belong to a Sram, but its powers left him in pieces."};
descriptions["15321"]={cn:"轻便和舒适的鞋子，让穿着他们的人能在冰上来去自如。",en:"These shoes are so light and comfortable that the participants of Prancing on Ice swear by them!"};
descriptions["15322"]={cn:"谁想得到帝王旋鸟竟然喜欢珠宝首饰？当他在时髦排队上翩翩起舞的时候，戒指会闪闪发光。",en:"Who knew the head of the Whirlies was such a fan of jewelry?! This one glints subtly as he twirls in and out of rooms at swanky parties."};
descriptions["15323"]={cn:"这是...旋鸟婚礼的...好日子！你看起来比拉森努斯·华莱士更像摇滚明星！",en:"It\'s a... nice day for a... Whirly weddiiing! YEAH! You look more rock \'n\' roll than Larsenus Wallace!"};
descriptions["15324"]={cn:"再也不会因为穿得不正式被拒之门外。来吧，来喱维萨的时髦夜总会吧！",en:"Goodbye, being turned away at the door for informal footwear; hello, Bilbiza\'s trendiest clubs!"};
descriptions["15325"]={cn:"亮丽光鲜，吸引着人群目光，使你成为舞会上最受瞩目的美女。穿上闪亮的胸衣和金闪闪的项链，你看上去比圣诞树还漂亮！",en:"This cloak sparkles and shines all over to make you the most questionably dressed belle at the ball.  Grab a shiny breastplate and a golden amulet and you\'ll look even better than the Kwismas tree!"};
descriptions["15326"]={cn:"这个头盔的内部都被旋鸟种子覆盖，这样可以保持这个你的头部一直处于舒适的状态。",en:"This helmet is covered in Whirly Seeds, which helps it fit snugly around heads of all shapes and sizes."};
descriptions["15327"]={cn:"这个护符让你看起来像是旋鸟们的国王。",en:"A lovely amulet to add to your collection!"};
descriptions["15328"]={cn:"腰上佩戴此件腰带不仅可以让你随意的扭动，还可以使你整夜都没有束缚感！我可真是个了不起的发明家。",en:"With this belt around your hips, you can twist and shout all night long! Why not change your name to Russell? Go wild!"};
descriptions["15329"]={cn:"终于，十年的苦功能派上用处了！",en:"Finally, ten years of baton twirling classes will pay off!"};
descriptions["15330"]={cn:"闪耀着神秘的红光，从时光漩涡迷雾中，唤醒强大力量。",en:"When used, this wand glimmers and glows with powers called forth from the swirling mists of time!"};
descriptions["15331"]={cn:"外观十分漂亮的卡牌，闪着诡异的光芒。你情不自禁地想打大老二。",en:"These cards look so pretty and whimsical when you drop them from a height that some people refuse to play anything but 52-Card Pickup with them."};
descriptions["15332"]={cn:"一旦插入受害者的体内，就不停旋转，能削下大片的肉。",en:"Once they\'ve been planted into their victim, these daggers continue to turn, just to carve as much meat as possible off their prey."};
descriptions["15333"]={cn:"它看起来像个婴儿漏斗，但是实际上它要比外表看起来有用的多。",en:"It looks like a baby space hopper, but in reality, it\'s used for much more serious things."};
descriptions["15335"]={cn:"前往地下城门口的兑奖机处兑换酷炫的奖励。",en:"Use the machine across from the dungeon to exchange your tokens for fantastic rewards."};
descriptions["15336"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["15337"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["15338"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["15339"]={cn:"仿佛置身于云层之中，舒适惬意。",en:"The observation that you have your head in the clouds is truer now than ever before."};
descriptions["15340"]={cn:"穿上它们，你会觉得仿佛在空中漫步，感觉自己变成小小的黄色圆球...是不是很眼熟？",en:"You feel like you\'re walking on air in these boots. You also feel like you\'re tiny, round and yellow... Sound familiar?"};
descriptions["15341"]={cn:"至少那些骑在你背后欺负你的混蛋现在有得受了。",en:"At least the school bully who pins you to the ground and sits on your back crowing triumphantly will be extra-comfortable now."};
descriptions["15342"]={cn:"既然你穿着这么漂亮的护肩，就不要再怪罪飞到你身上的咕咕了。",en:"With shoulders as comfy-looking as yours, you can hardly blame all the little Piwis for coming to perch on you!"};
descriptions["15343"]={cn:"该腰带赢得了本年度十二世界最舒适腰带奖。你真幸运！",en:"This belt won the World of Twelve\'s Most Comfortable Belt award this year. You bandwagon jumper, you."};
descriptions["15344"]={cn:"请注意胸甲内侧的洗标！如果洗涤时太过用力，羽毛会掉落下来，只留下一张光溜溜的豆芙皮。",en:"Make sure you pay attention to the washing guidelines on the seam of this breastplate! If you wash it too hard, the feathers will come out, leaving you with a loose-fitting corset of irritated Tofu skin."};
descriptions["15345"]={cn:"起飞去天界领地之前，不要忘了系紧腰带。",en:"Don\'t forget to belt up before you take off for the celestial promised land."};
descriptions["15346"]={cn:"务必置放于阴凉避光处。让你脖子细腻红润有光泽。",en:"This amulet will evaporate if you stay too long in a hot, dry place. Your cold, clammy neck will be fine, though."};
descriptions["15347"]={cn:"如果你意志薄弱，抵不住诱惑想盖着披风打个盹。你会永远都不想醒来。它实在太舒服了！",en:"If you do succumb to the temptation to take a nap in this cloak, please beware that you probably won\'t ever get up again. It\'s so cosy!"};
descriptions["15348"]={cn:"在天界豆芙的小时候，他曾经为唤兽师当过信差。当时他用这戒指来封信封。",en:"Back in the Celestial Tofu\'s humbler days, when he was just a mail boy for Osamodas, he used this ring to seal the envelopes."};
descriptions["15349"]={cn:"这对护肩是由天界豆芙的脚掌制成的。但是没有人想到他居然会穿着袜子和沙滩鞋。",en:"These epaulettes were based on the feet of the Celestial Tofu himself. I know right, I never thought he\'d wear socks with sandals either."};
descriptions["15350"]={cn:"孕育了神圣豆芙双胞胎...豆芙鲁斯和德芙斯。",en:"These epaulettes were the cradles of two twin Divine Tofus: Tofulus and Tefus."};
descriptions["15351"]={cn:"当神圣豆芙准备拿着这枚戒指向心爱的豆芙妮求婚的时候，他发现她躺在别人的羽毛床上...",en:"The Celestial Tofu was just about to offer this ring to his sweetheart when he found out that she\'d been laying eggs in other feather beds..."};
descriptions["15352"]={cn:"据说护符的拥有者会永享安宁。比起龙蛋，奥古真应该拿它去讨好女人。",en:"The owner of this amulet is said to be granted divine eternal rest. Ogrest probably should have gone for one of these rather than those pesky Dofus."};
descriptions["15353"]={cn:"想装天使的话只要把腰带顶在头上就可以了。",en:"Doubles up as a halo if ever you have to fake your own death."};
descriptions["15354"]={cn:"把你的猎物绑起来，用这根羽毛去挠他的胸脯。对于男人来说绝对是最残酷的刑罚！",en:"Tie your prey up and tickle its chin with this feather! It\'s the most harrowing torture known to man!"};
descriptions["15355"]={cn:"为了往胸甲上粘上羽毛，耗费了无数豆芙便便，想想都觉得恶心。",en:"Just imagine how many kagallons of Tofu droppings had to be used to stick all the feathers onto this breastplate!"};
descriptions["15356"]={cn:"哼嗯嗯...没有人知道你的豆芙猎物午餐吃了些什么，但是从臀部的情况来看，它吃的东西不太新鲜。",en:"Hmmm... Nobody knows for sure what the last thing your Tofu prey ate, but from the looks of this rump, it wasn\'t very fresh."};
descriptions["15357"]={cn:"今年的豆芙狂欢节上，再也不用为没有合适的时装发愁了。戴上这只鸟嘴，你准备好了。",en:"If the Too Faux Karnaval creeps up on you again this year, don\'t worry about not having an elaborate costume. Stick this beak on and you\'re ready to go."};
descriptions["15359"]={cn:"留着这么拉风的发型，所有的孩子们都会崇拜你。只是千万别去卷风村。那里的大风会把你的假发吹飞。",en:"With a hairstyle like this, you\'ll have teens falling at your feet the World over. Except, perhaps, in the Windy Village. You wouldn\'t set foot there if your life depended on it."};
descriptions["15360"]={cn:"建议随身携带，以防你的宠物随地方便。",en:"Always carry it with you in case your pet gets a little too excited."};
descriptions["15361"]={cn:"宠物染料可以于宠物设定介面中更改。此物品已无用处，可以将其分解掉。",en:"Pet colorings can be changed in the pet settings interface. This item is obsolete; you can recycle it."};
descriptions["15362"]={cn:"这堆鸟粪对于治疗皮肤干燥有奇效。你是第一个尝试疗效的！",en:"These droppings are said to have divine properties if you apply them generously to your skin. Are you ready to accept the challenge?"};
descriptions["15363"]={cn:"好好使用这件披风。成百上千的豆芙千辛万苦地长大，贡献了它们的羽毛，只为完成这件奢侈品。你亏欠豆芙太多！",en:"Take good care of this cloak. You owe that much at least to the hundreds of Tofus who carefully grew and groomed their feathers just to make a luxury cloak."};
descriptions["15364"]={cn:"看起来很一般，但是盾不可貌相。如果能使用方法正确，大师级弓手也无法伤害到你。",en:"This shield isn\'t much to look at, but don\'t judge a book by its cover. Use it right and not even a master Cra will get to you."};
descriptions["15365"]={cn:"大幅提高跑步速度，已经有数位运动员因为穿这双靴子被酷洛运动会除名了。",en:"Several athletes have already been disqualified from the Krozolympiks for wearing these boots, which greatly increase runners\' speed."};
descriptions["15366"]={cn:"依附着一只胖芙的灵魂。",en:"This amulet contains the soul of a Tofurby. You probably already knew that, judging by its name and its imposing appearance."};
descriptions["15367"]={cn:"你屡次尝试为匕首抛光，但是上面的便便总是擦不掉，仿佛在说“我们先来的”。你只好学着和它们分享空间，并且经常洗手。",en:"You\'ve tried and tried to polish this dagger, but the droppings on it seem to proclaim, \'We were here first!\' You\'ll just have to learn how to share, and start washing your hands more often."};
descriptions["15368"]={cn:"你居然找到了这张藏宝图！艾卡菲利神一定对你青睐有加。现在你只需要解开这张地图的秘密就可以了。",en:"Ecaflip must be smiling down upon you, for you hold in your hands one of the Captains\' treasure maps. Now you just have to decipher it..."};
