descriptions["15384"]={cn:"宠物装备可以于宠物设定介面中更改。此物品已无用处，可以将其分解掉。",en:"Pet equipment can be changed in the pet settings interface. This item is obsolete; you can recycle it."};
descriptions["15385"]={cn:"宠物装备可以于宠物设定介面中更改。此物品已无用处，可以将其分解掉。",en:"Pet equipment can be changed in the pet settings interface. This item is obsolete; you can recycle it."};
descriptions["15386"]={cn:"宠物装备可以于宠物设定介面中更改。此物品已无用处，可以将其分解掉。",en:"Pet equipment can be changed in the pet settings interface. This item is obsolete; you can recycle it."};
descriptions["15387"]={cn:"宠物装备可以于宠物设定介面中更改。此物品已无用处，可以将其分解掉。",en:"Pet equipment can be changed in the pet settings interface. This item is obsolete; you can recycle it."};
descriptions["15388"]={cn:"作腿也很烦！每天都要被人掰来掰去，动不动还要参加什么二人三腿比赛...",en:"Sometimes, Chafer Legs that have been forcibly separated from their original owners develop a liking for passing adventurers and engage them in involuntary three-legged races."};
descriptions["15389"]={cn:"能在任何物体上咬出一个洞来，无论是爱鱿肢体还是宝藏猎人的干巴脚板。",en:"This fang will pierce a neat hole in any kind of material, be it soft Kralove flesh or the dry skin on the bottom of an Enutrof\'s foot."};
descriptions["15391"]={cn:"有的人（尤其是唤兽师）认为扒捣蛋兽的皮太残忍了，实际情况是它们柔软又舒适，是时尚男士的必备佳品。还等什么，去搞一双吧。",en:"Some people, especially Osamodas, find these shoes cruel, but they\'re soft, comfy and the coolest thing since guys wearing one earring, so you have to have at least one pair."};
descriptions["15392"]={cn:"为不安分的地穴兽专门设计。你需要做的只是把它戴上爱宠的脖子，然后就可以安心睡眠了！",en:"This amulet was designed with sleepless Drhellers in mind. All you had to do was slip it around your beloved pet\'s neck for a peaceful, refreshing night!"};
descriptions["15393"]={cn:"拥有它的主人值得骄傲。原本指环是为捣蛋兽设计的，目的是为了防止它变成瞎眼的杀戮机器！",en:"The wearer of this bracelet should be very proud. It was originally intended as a muzzle for Rascal, and it was the only thing that stopped him from being a busy, dizzy, killing machine!"};
descriptions["15394"]={cn:"锁...锁...锁链之靴！小心，这些链条都在动！也许这双靴子的存在是对所有你击败动物的惩罚的象征...",en:"Ch-ch-ch-ch-chained boots! Look out, you rock and roller! Maybe this is punishment for all the victims you\'ve killed in your days..."};
descriptions["15395"]={cn:"制造这把武器的匠人工作了整整九天九夜将捣蛋兽牙改造成指针。",en:"The craftsman who made this weapon had to work for nine days and nine nights to turn a Rascal Tusk into a hand."};
descriptions["15396"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["15397"]={cn:"穿上它，四肢着地，像个真正的野兽一样攻击你的敌人。",en:"This cloak will make sure you stay stylish as you paw the ground and charge your enemy like a wild beast."};
descriptions["15398"]={cn:"护肩上的鬃毛据说像地穴兽的牙齿一样锋利...又或者也许是犄角？我记不清了。反正它们都很锋利。",en:"The tufts on these epaulettes are supposed to represent the Drheller\'s sharp teeth... Or was it the horns? I can\'t remember. They hurt a lot, either way!"};
descriptions["15399"]={cn:"捣蛋兽刚出生时戴过这只戒指。但是它现在戴不下了。它现在是个大家伙。",en:"Rascal used to wear this ring as a bracelet when he was a newborn. He can\'t wear it any more, though, can he? He\'s a big boy now! Who\'s a big, bad Drheller?"};
descriptions["15400"]={cn:"由捣蛋兽皮制成，适用于任何地形。无论是布拉克玛的火山坡还是阿玛克纳的泥泞沼泽，都将如履平地。",en:"These boots were fashioned out of Rascal Leather and are hardy companions for all types of terrain, from Brakmar\'s volcanic slopes to the muddy marshlands of Amakna!"};
descriptions["15401"]={cn:"和挺起的肚腩说再见吧！",en:"The instructions on the packet say that, if you hit your enemy in just the right spot, some of his body parts will pop right out! But where...? Now, that\'s the question."};
descriptions["15402"]={cn:"鼠家族好不容易东拼西凑，缝了件衣服...",en:"This breastplate was cobbled together using patches of fabric and armor from all the members of the Rat family."};
descriptions["15403"]={cn:"鼠太后传下来的戒指，不知道哪位姑娘有幸能戴上。",en:"This ring used to belong to Ratical\'s mother. Apparently, whoever\'s wearing it is the life and soul of the party!"};
descriptions["15404"]={cn:"用鼠王及其党羽的肢体制成。多数敢用的人根本不知道护盾的原料。",en:"This shield is made up of all the body parts that were left over after one of Ratical\'s riotous parties. If you can bear to carry it, you probably don\'t realize that\'s what it\'s made of."};
descriptions["15405"]={cn:"它发出什么样的声音一定取决于你使用这把武器敲击身体的不同部位，咯吱...噗通...咔嚓！",en:"This stick makes a variety of different sounds, depending on which part of the body you hit with it. Ra ta boink tish ta rata ta taka!"};
descriptions["15406"]={cn:"当侯媛夫人发明出这种工具来清理落叶后，斯拉斯拉德先生已经迫不及待的借来用作清理他敌人的遗骸了，一个也不能落下。",en:"When Lady Gardenmore invented this tool for gathering dead leaves into piles, Sir Slayalday couldn\'t wait to borrow it to do the same thing with enemies\' corpses. Each to their own."};
descriptions["15407"]={cn:"你越是勒紧这个腰带，它就会变的越宽松，并不是因为有什么恶意，而是它本身就很有趣。",en:"The tighter you pull this belt, the wider it will smile. It serves no purpose whatsoever, but it\'s pretty funny."};
descriptions["15408"]={cn:"看起来像是不错的美食，实际上只是收集来的资源！",en:"This looks like a fantastic meal, but it\'s actually a resource harvested from... *gulp*... Ratical\'s stinky feet!"};
descriptions["15409"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["15410"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["15411"]={cn:"老鼠也穿运动夹克么？是不是防水还防臭吧！",en:"We all know about arrow-proof jackets, but have you heard about beer-proof cardigans? This one gives you a shock for each swig you take. Electrifying!"};
descriptions["15412"]={cn:"即使做成了标本，生前的口臭仍旧在一阵阵地散发出来。戴着它上街的话，请务必远离人群。",en:"This rat may be stuffed, but the halitosis it suffered in life has become stronger than ever in death. When you\'re walking around town, you part crowds without even trying!"};
descriptions["15413"]={cn:"围在胸前就是围兜兜了，闻着味道不错哦！",en:"Whip this cloak round to the front and you can use it as a bib. To be honest, the smell coming off it is making you drool already..."};
descriptions["15414"]={cn:"别怕，不是虫子，看起来像而已...其实，是老鼠尾巴...",en:"Oh, don\'t worry, it\'s not a worm! It\'s just a hairless, creepy, squidgy rat tail. Watch out for splinters!"};
descriptions["15415"]={cn:"戴上这顶头盔，过街老鼠都会向你脱帽致敬。",en:"With any luck, this piece will be enough to have the rats bowing down before you. You might need to take a bath in the sewers just to make the costume more authentic, though."};
descriptions["15416"]={cn:"这条护符的作用是保证你能笔直向前飞...当然，没人敢保证你不撞到墙...",en:"This amulet\'s goal is to keep you on the straight and narrow... Although, judging by the direction you\'ve taken so far, I\'m not sure going straight on is ideal..."};
descriptions["15417"]={cn:"在令人昏昏欲睡的会议上咬你一口，使你保持清醒...",en:"This breastplate will stop you from shaking with nerves at important meetings... as well as giving you an electric shock if you find yourself falling asleep!"};
descriptions["15418"]={cn:"并不能让你飞得更快，只能让你以更快的速度坠落...",en:"If ever you\'re unlucky enough to topple off a tall, iconic clock... Well, these heavy boots are only going to speed up your fall."};
descriptions["15419"]={cn:"这双靴子在脚后跟处配备了一组自动巡航模块，帮助你从酒馆出来之后顺利回到家里。",en:"These boots have an auto-pilot module installed in the heels. No more getting lost when you try to walk home from the tavern!"};
descriptions["15450"]={cn:"曾经属于胡埃·斯特劳德的地穴兽。如果贪婪的宝藏猎人看到你带着它，他会疯狂地用铲子追打你，让你好几周眼冒豆芙！",en:"This collar used to sit proudly around the neck of Ruel Stroud\'s Drheller. If the greedy Enutrof sees you with it, he\'ll hit you so hard with his shovel that you\'ll be seeing Tofus for weeks!"};
descriptions["15451"]={cn:"据说一只地穴兽和一只皮皮结合了，他们生出了长着尖刺的地穴兽...真爱无敌，不是吗？",en:"They say the spines on this breastplate can be explained by the fusion of a Drheller and a Prespic... Nothing can get in the way of true love, eh?"};
descriptions["15452"]={cn:"让你的庇护袋里面看起来神圣一点，蒸汽行者必备。",en:"This sacred table will look great in your crib. Especially if you\'re a Foggernaut."};
descriptions["15453"]={cn:"让你的庇护袋里面看起来神圣一点，刺客必备。",en:"This sacred table will look great in your crib. Especially if you\'re a descendant of the god Sram."};
descriptions["15454"]={cn:"让你的庇护袋里面看起来神圣一点，熊猫武僧必备。",en:"This sacred table will look great in your crib, especially if you\'re a descendant of the goddess Pandawa."};
descriptions["15455"]={cn:"让你的庇护袋里面看起来神圣一点，唤兽师必备。",en:"This sacred table will look great in your crib. Especially if you\'re a descendant of the god Osamodas."};
descriptions["15456"]={cn:"让你的庇护袋里面看起来神圣一点，守护者必备。",en:"This sacred table will look great in your crib, especially if you\'re a descendant of the goddess Feca."};
descriptions["15457"]={cn:"让你的庇护袋里面看起来神圣一点，盗贼必备。",en:"This sacred table will look great in your crib. Especially if you love bombs."};
descriptions["15462"]={cn:"如果你稍微无私一点，你可以用它来清理海滩上的垃圾，而不是动不动就夹无辜路人的屁股。",en:"If you were a little less shellfish, you might use this thing to clear the beach of garbage rather than just pinching innocent by-standers\' butts with it."};
descriptions["15463"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["15464"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["15465"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["15467"]={cn:"你的对手看到这顶帽子，会想一会儿才攻击你。",en:"Upon seeing this hat, your opponents will think twice before attacking you."};
descriptions["15468"]={cn:"这顶帽子见证了你与狂怒豆芙的相遇与别离。",en:"This hat bears witness to your encounter with the Enraged Tofu, and to the way in which it ended."};
descriptions["15469"]={cn:"当你望向它的双眼，你会觉得它想要攻击你。",en:"When you look it in the eyes, you get the feeling it\'s going to attack."};
descriptions["15470"]={cn:"一枚由豆芙的愤怒浓缩而成的护符。",en:"An amulet made from concentrated Tofu anger."};
descriptions["15471"]={cn:"小心拧紧它，不然它们可能会试着逃跑的。",en:"Tighten it properly, otherwise it may try to escape."};
descriptions["15472"]={cn:"这条腰带仍然带着它前任主人的怒火而振动着。",en:"This belt is still vibrating with the rage of its former owner."};
descriptions["15473"]={cn:"冲向你的敌人 - 它们无机可乘。",en:"Rush at your enemy - they won\'t stand a chance."};
descriptions["15474"]={cn:"将你的手指套在如此野性的指环之内，需要相当大的勇气。",en:"You need to be brave to dare put your finger in such a wild ring."};
descriptions["15475"]={cn:"这野性的指环毫无约束感。",en:"This wild-natured ring knows no restraint."};
descriptions["15476"]={cn:"这双靴子很适合在人世间留下你的足迹...在敌人脸上也行。",en:"These boots are really practically to make marks on the ground... or on your opponent\'s face."};
descriptions["15477"]={cn:"这是你能找到的最好的靴子了。你不这么说的话，这双靴子就会跳起来踢你。",en:"You\'ll never find better boots than these. If you claim otherwise, they\'ll attack you."};
descriptions["15478"]={cn:"这双靴子会让你跑的特别快，哪怕你脑袋已经被砍下来了。",en:"These boots will let you run very fast, even if you\'ve been beheaded."};
descriptions["15479"]={cn:"这件豆芙肩时尚时尚最时尚，让人情不自禁的摩擦摩擦。",en:"With such a swanky piece of kit, it\'s difficult to keep your head on your shoulders!"};
descriptions["15480"]={cn:"这件斗篷散发的怪味之野性...举世无双。",en:"Nothing\'s wilder than the odor of this cloak."};
descriptions["15481"]={cn:"当心别仰天倒下，会爬不起来的。",en:"Careful you don\'t fall on your back wearing this cape. You\'ll never get up again."};
descriptions["15482"]={cn:"盘丝怪结的网再大，也能用这个掸子轻松掸除。",en:"Great for sweeping up even the biggest Arachnoshima webs."};
descriptions["15483"]={cn:"这双可恶的靴子总是让你忍不住想横着走。",en:"Annoyingly, these boots often get their kicks out of making you walk sideways."};
descriptions["15484"]={cn:"狂怒豆芙的狂怒全部凝聚到了这副坚固的胸甲之中。",en:"The entire fury of an Enraged Tofu is concentrated into this tough armor."};
descriptions["15485"]={cn:"如果你能忍受蟹脚在你身上爬的话，这会是市面上最好的护符。",en:"This amulet is the best on the market, if you enjoy the feeling of tiny feet crawling all over you."};
descriptions["15486"]={cn:"你浑身散发着海洋的气息。你该考虑下为旅行社工作了。",en:"You could work for the tourist board with that seaside smell following you everywhere you go."};
descriptions["15487"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["15488"]={cn:"能穿透你双耳的帽子。你最好随身携带防腐剂。",en:"A hat that also pierces your ears. Always carry antiseptic cream with you."};
descriptions["15489"]={cn:"敌人会吓得泪流成河。",en:"The only sword you need to make your enemies cry you a river."};
descriptions["15490"]={cn:"将那只螃蟹做成护肩而不是意大利面是正确的选择。虽然你现在有些想吃水草...",en:"You just want to take these Although you would kill for a sandwich right now."};
descriptions["15491"]={cn:"我有个朋友曾经有一根这样的腰带。她喜欢嚼蟹肉棒，然后对我指手画脚。我们再也不是朋友了。",en:"My friend used to have one of these. He was constantly chewing on pieces of Cwab Stick and breathing down my neck. We\'re not friends any more."};
descriptions["15492"]={cn:"尖锐的小东西被恶魔依附着，它不放弃任何机会，攻击一切事物。我是你的话，情愿把它插在针扎上。",en:"This sharp little thing definitely has demons to lay to rest, as it pricks anything it can at the slightest opportunity. I\'d keep it stuck in a pin cushion if I were you."};
descriptions["15493"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，而且很潮湿。",en:"Portable, easy to assemble, and very, very wet."};
descriptions["15494"]={cn:"仔细看看，看到了什么？别说只有脏兮兮的污渍...",en:"What do you see when you look into this cloak? Don\'t just say splodges, I want to get inside your head..."};
descriptions["15495"]={cn:"显然狼祭司曾经用这只蟹钳来整理幼狼的鬃毛。她有点笨手笨脚的，不是吗？",en:"Apparently the Boowolfine used this very pincer to trim her Miliboowolves\' manes. She didn\'t do a very good job of it, did she?"};
descriptions["15496"]={cn:"浸湿的时候比较漂亮...相信我，没错的。",en:"This belt would look better down where it\'s wetter - take it from me."};
descriptions["15497"]={cn:"妥善保管这件披风。我的朋友有一件，但是他把披风忘在了阳光下，融化了。",en:"Be very careful with this cloak. A friend of mine had one, but he left it out in the sun and it vanished."};
descriptions["15498"]={cn:"肩膀上戴着甲吾和甲汝两兄弟。它们谁会先出手呢？两个都不会，它们都很烂。",en:"Pinchmie and Pinchyu are on your shoulders. Which one will strike first? Probably neither; they both kind of suck."};
descriptions["15499"]={cn:"看见手杖上的牙印了吗？奥古曾经把它误认为食物。他脑子不太灵光...",en:"See the tooth marks all over this staff? Well, Ogrest once mistook it for something edible. Not very bright, is he...?"};
descriptions["15501"]={cn:"那是...？我想是的...！瀑布！！！",en:"Is that a...? I think it is...! WATERFAAAALL!!!"};
descriptions["15502"]={cn:"因为你刚装在肩膀上的滑梯，你头上的虱子们决定选你做本月最佳市民。它们正在申请建个游泳池。",en:"Just so you know, your head lice have voted you Citizen of the Month for the slides you installed on your shoulders, and are now petitioning for a swimming pool."};
descriptions["15503"]={cn:"据说可以在沙漠中变出水来...你想去沙漠试试吗？",en:"Legend has it that this amulet can make water appear in desert regions... Are you really willing to go there to find out if it\'s true?"};
descriptions["15504"]={cn:"白天的潇洒短裤，夜晚的销魂草裙。堪称完美。",en:"A kingly belt for the daytime; a hula skirt for the evening. Perfect!"};
descriptions["15505"]={cn:"觉得热？脱下裤子穿这条腰带就行了。",en:"It may not provide water when it gets really hot, but it does let the air circulate freely around your undercarriage."};
descriptions["15506"]={cn:"据说这条腰带曾经属于一个有名的布丁...但是没有人记得住它的名字。",en:"It\'s said that this belt used to belong to a famous Puddly... but everyone\'s forgotten his name."};
descriptions["15507"]={cn:"半夜起来如果发现队友在围着你载歌载舞，不要觉得奇怪。",en:"Don\'t be surprised when you wake up in the middle of the night to find your team mates dancing around your head, chanting."};
descriptions["15508"]={cn:"带着这枚戒指入睡，醒来会发现手指上起了很多小泡泡。",en:"He who falls asleep with Imperial Puddly Ring, wakes up with soggy finger."};
descriptions["15509"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，而且很潮湿。",en:"Portable, easy to assemble, and very, very wet."};
descriptions["15510"]={cn:"在又滑又粘的液体全漏掉之前，请尽快用掉。",en:"Use this flask up quickly before its moist, gelatinous contents leak out in their entirety."};
descriptions["15512"]={cn:"你几乎...可以在水上行走。",en:"The closest you\'ll ever get to walking on water."};
descriptions["15513"]={cn:"值得信任的匕首，只是有股便便味而已。",en:"A pair of trusty daggers, just dripping with malice and bird droppings."};
descriptions["15514"]={cn:"颜色鲜明而温暖，能让你不知不觉就联想起农场的景象，不管是咕咕叫还是睡在木梁上，它通通能够实现。",en:"Warm, yellow, and somehow reminiscent of the farmyard, these are the shoes for you if you enjoy clucking stupidly, sleeping on thin wooden beams, and totally nailing the alphabet."};
descriptions["15515"]={cn:"西方最强装备...曾经是，现在么，有点生锈啦，不过拿来抵挡野兽的撕咬完全没问题。",en:"These epaulettes used to be the best in the west! Today, they\'re a little rusty, but they can still hold their own in the pecking order."};
descriptions["15516"]={cn:"一只啾啾对另一只啾啾说：啾啾...啾啾啾...啾啾啾啾...啾...啾啾...啾啾啾...",en:"One Piwi says to another Piwi, \"Piwipiwipiwi!\" The second replies, \"Hey, quit stealing my line!\""};
descriptions["15517"]={cn:"没有人知道天界啾啾究竟吃了什么。但是这便便的气味一定不是这世界上的。",en:"I don\'t know what the Piwis are eating up there, but the stench is out of this world."};
descriptions["15518"]={cn:"这枚指环所散发出的臭味足以让你一个植物术士提前六个月进入冬眠状态。",en:"This ring emits an odor so strong that it could send a Sadida into hibernation six months early."};
descriptions["15519"]={cn:"只要这把武器在手，你就再也不用因为半夜闯入墓地时惊扰到周围邻居而烦恼了。",en:"With this weapon in hand, you\'ll be able to venture into the cemetery at any time of night without the slightest trouble from the residents."};
descriptions["15520"]={cn:"外表会骗人，气味可不会：你还是不要知道这根外表纯洁的毛是从狂怒豆芙的哪个部位拔下来的了...",en:"Appearances can be deceptive, trust your sense of smell: it\'s probably better you don\'t know which end of the Tofu this immaculate feather was pulled from."};
descriptions["15522"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["15523"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["15524"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["15525"]={cn:"哦啦啦，哦咧咧，哦啾啾。",en:"Ooh rah, ooh la la! My Cloudy Piwat! - Brrrbley Spears"};
descriptions["15526"]={cn:"即便你身披斗篷、内裤外穿，也别想飞起来。",en:"Just so you know, the trendy \"feather-and-wing\" design on this cape won\'t be enough to save you when you leap off the cliff edge, hoping to soar across Amakna like a bird."};
descriptions["15527"]={cn:"尺寸偏大，去店里修一下吧。",en:"If these epaulettes are the wrong size, just head down to the shop on Piwidilly Circus to get them adjusted."};
descriptions["15528"]={cn:"枕头大战的时候正好拿来穿着。",en:"When you tire of this breastplate, you\'ll be able to use it as reinforcement in your Piwillow fort!"};
descriptions["15529"]={cn:"上等羽毛制成，让你健步如飞。",en:"These boots are lined with anti-perspirant feathers to provide your aching feet with a little light relief."};
descriptions["15530"]={cn:"好柔软！不知道的话还以为是厕纸做得呢！",en:"This belt is so soft! If you didn\'t know any better, you\'d think it was made of luxury toilet paper."};
descriptions["15531"]={cn:"又轻又软，人见人爱。谁给差评谁就是秃顶的宝藏猎人。",en:"Light and soft, this hat definitely won\'t make your hair wear thin. Any bad reviews it gets come from Enutrofs who were already balding long ago."};
descriptions["15532"]={cn:"不是所有穿披风的人都能飞的，你至少还需要内裤外穿。",en:"No, no, this won\'t grant you the power of flight. I said... Argh... Do what you like, then."};
descriptions["15533"]={cn:"便宜好用。",en:"Cheep and cheerful."};
descriptions["15534"]={cn:"高贵品质，时尚典范。一定是约翰·阿尼玛设计的。",en:"Such elegance! Such style! A bodice like this simply must have been designed by John Piwi Googooltier."};
descriptions["15535"]={cn:"名字很强力的感觉，功能一定也...你想多了。",en:"You\'d think that boots with a name as heavenly as these would have been cleaned beforehand... But no."};
descriptions["15536"]={cn:"是的，你把手指塞进了一个指环里，但愿只是一个指环...",en:"Yes, you did just stuff your finger into a ring of bird poop, but it\'s fine, because it\'s organic."};
descriptions["15537"]={cn:"所有的啾啾当初为了把名字刻在这个手镯上，排队等了三天三夜。可是他们都叫啾啾，而这是个咕咕手镯...",en:"All the Piwis lined up to have their names engraved on this bangle, but since they\'re all called \"Piwi\", it became somewhat pointless."};
descriptions["15538"]={cn:"上面刻着一只啾啾。不幸的是，她好像跌到鸟粪里了。",en:"There\'s an engraving of Mother Piwi on this amulet. Unfortunately, she seems to have fallen into a heap of guano. Too bad."};
descriptions["15539"]={cn:"来，把两只手用弓弦打个结，这样你就厉害啦！做不到？那就用来射射箭吧，也算挺管用的。",en:"If you wriggle both your arms through the gap in this bow, you might gain the power of flight! For the moment, it would be safer just to shoot arrows from it, though."};
descriptions["15540"]={cn:"像玩风车一样在面前用力挥舞，没有牛蝇（或者其他什么飞虫）再敢阻拦你了。",en:"Twirl this in circles in front of you like a windmill, and you can guarantee that no Moofly - or anything else for that matter - will dare get in your way."};
descriptions["15542"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["15543"]={cn:"把这只鸵鸟做成护肩是明智的选择，上面肯定有某种病菌。",en:"You made a good choice turning that Strich into epaulettes rather than nuggets. It definitely had some kind of disease."};
descriptions["15544"]={cn:"你将成为全省哞业大赛的焦点。你说什么？你不想去？",en:"You\'ll be the star of the Regional Moogrriculturual Convention in this finery. What do you mean you\'re not going? You have to go!"};
descriptions["15545"]={cn:"免费给你为期一年的本地哞业协会成员资格。这意味着...可以免费喝牛奶啦！",en:"This amulet grants you one year\'s membership to the Regional Moogricultural Society, and you know what that means... FREE PEN!"};
descriptions["15546"]={cn:"100%天然胸甲，让你自主选择。你到底会选择带刺的那一面还是比较粘的那一面？",en:"This 100% reversible breastplate lets YOU make the big decisions in life! Will you choose... the scratchy side... or the sticky side?!"};
descriptions["15547"]={cn:"太瘦了！对孕育哞崽没有好处！",en:"Too skinny! Not good for bearing Moogrroons."};
descriptions["15548"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["15549"]={cn:"谈恋爱，跟哞哞哞...哞！！！哞！！！哞哞哞！！！",en:"Mooo!!! Mooo!!! Mooooooooooooo!!!"};
descriptions["15550"]={cn:"靠着这对宽大可靠的护肩，可以成为团队核心...所有人都喜欢在你的肩膀上嚎啕大哭。",en:"Become the \"rock\" of the team with these large, dependable epaulettes - everyone\'s favorite shoulder to cry on."};
descriptions["15551"]={cn:"胸毛迎风吹，日升映晨晖。",en:"Nothing like some hair on your chest to prepare you for a new day."};
descriptions["15552"]={cn:"穿上这个就跟鸵鸟差不多了，小心猎人把你当真的打了。哦，忘了你喜欢被人追着跑了。",en:"Strich hunters will almost definitely mistake you for one of their prey if you wear this. Maybe you like having men chase after you, though."};
descriptions["15553"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["15554"]={cn:"一枚显眼的勋章掉落在布拉克玛废弃的鸵鸟笼子里，以前的人们建造了这个大型的鸟笼来保存它的标本。",en:"An eye-catching medallion scooped off the floor in the Abandoned Strichery in Brakmar. The Governor who built the birdcage saved it for his finest specimens."};
descriptions["15555"]={cn:"你走运了，前主人在卖掉戒指前用它擤过鼻涕。这样你的手指可以顺畅地戴上它。",en:"As luck would have it, this ring\'s ex-owner sneezed through it before putting it up for sale. So your finger slips in with no trouble at all."};
descriptions["15556"]={cn:"由一支骑士乐队所命名，他们觉得敌人被棒槌击打胃部之后放出的声音很好玩...",en:"This bat was named by a band of Iops, who were amused by the sound their enemies emitted as the weapon struck them in the stomach."};
descriptions["15557"]={cn:"你浑身散发着一股牛骚味。你一定很喜欢这股气味！",en:"Wear a Moomulet and you\'ll be wreathed in a Moogrrish smell all the time. Just what you always wanted!"};
descriptions["15558"]={cn:"不用等到夏天再展现你的肌肉了！古尔塔看见了这件胸甲会眼红得流口水！",en:"No need to wait til summer to show off your pecs! They\'re enough to make Goultard drool."};
descriptions["15559"]={cn:"让冒险者拥有强健的骨骼和身躯，虽然冒险者大都很短命。",en:"This Mimilk helps the adventurer build strong bones and a sturdy constitution, all the way up to the end of his short life."};
descriptions["15560"]={cn:"印着鸵鸟贵族的皇家徽记。很值钱么？",en:"Royal trappings for a prize-winning Strich. Are you really wothy?"};
descriptions["15561"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["15562"]={cn:"如果有人在你戴着这顶帽子的时候说你“鸵鸟脸”的话，他们是完全正确的！",en:"If someone called you \"Strich-face\" while you\'re wearing this headgear... well, they\'d be entirely right!"};
descriptions["15563"]={cn:"你费了吃奶的力气才把这戒指从那只该死的鸵鸟腿上弄下来。于是你自豪地戴着它，时刻铭记不要脸的毅力才是王道。",en:"You went through hell and high water to wrestle this ring off that blasted Strich. Wear it proudly and never forget that perseverance is the key."};
descriptions["15564"]={cn:"那些小混混再也不会麻烦你了！要讹钱，想都别想！送你几根羽毛回家插头发去！",en:"Those bullies won\'t bother you now! After years without a hair on your chest, now you have a proud, feathery chest wig!"};
descriptions["15565"]={cn:"为什么你最讨厌被别人挑刺，同时一旦有机会却最起劲地挑别人的刺？",en:"Why is it that you hate being criticized by others, but the moment you get the chance, you\'re the most critical of the lot?"};
descriptions["15566"]={cn:"漂亮极了...对鸵鸟来说是不是太高贵了？",en:"What a dandy neckpiece... Isn\'t it a bit too grand for a Strich?"};
descriptions["15567"]={cn:"点击两下来把整组古代资源转换成新的资源。古代资源需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["15568"]={cn:"就算你头上有沙子，路人仍然会被你脚上的靴子所吸引。",en:"Even when you have your head in the sand, passers-by will be able to admire your finest footwear."};
descriptions["15569"]={cn:"让你真正了解鸵鸟家族。",en:"This belt will have you well and truly in Striches."};
descriptions["15570"]={cn:"天上掉下的鸟粪太多，所以这面护盾只是拿来当伞用。",en:"Admittedly, there\'s so much bird poop around here that this shield is more useful as an umbrella than anything else."};
descriptions["15571"]={cn:"手持这柄铲子，清除屋子前恶心的布丁。",en:"Always have this shovel on hand to clear the path in front of your house of nasty puddles."};
descriptions["15574"]={cn:"我见过的最漂亮的大斧。",en:"Snakes alive! This is the nicest axe I\'ve ever seen!"};
descriptions["15578"]={cn:"虽然当你的手指肿胀时不推荐这枚戒指，但是即使佩戴者的手指没有肿胀，它也确实会让人感到恼火。",en:"Although this ring is not advised if you have fingers that swell, it does have the annoying habit of making its wearer furious even if they do not have fingers that swell."};
descriptions["15579"]={cn:"多亏这个护身符，你将发现埋藏在你内心深处的愤怒！",en:"Thanks to this amulet, you\'ll discover the rage buried inside you!"};
descriptions["15580"]={cn:"如果这条腰带不是因为它太丑而有独到之处，那它就真的没什么意思了。",en:"If this belt\'s particularity wasn\'t that it\'s so ugly, it really would be of no interest."};
descriptions["15582"]={cn:"这双靴子在牧场上提供了无与伦比的嬉戏速度。在城市里，其他人会对这种气味有意见。",en:"This boots provide unequaled frolicking speed in the pastures. In the city, other people will settle for commenting on the odor."};
descriptions["15584"]={cn:"避免在田野里穿这件斗篷，除非你想让一群绵球来袭击你。",en:"Avoid wearing this cape in a field, unless you want a flock of Gobballs to descend upon you."};
descriptions["15585"]={cn:"金苹朵哦金苹朵，大家都来咬一口！",en:"I\'ve got a Golden Api! I\'ve got a golden twinkle in my eye! Have a bite!"};
descriptions["15587"]={cn:"这件胸甲无与伦比地坚固。然而，其中一些部分似乎被饿过头的啾啾啄掉了。",en:"This breastplate\'s sturdiness is unequaled. However, it seems that some of them have been pecked away at by especially hungry Piwis."};
descriptions["15588"]={cn:"为了达到这样的效果，十二世界的工匠们不得不联合起来。看看结果，你得问问自己有多少人参加了。",en:"To achieve such a result, the craftsmen of the World of Twelve had to team up. Looking at the result, you have to ask yourself how many of them took part."};
descriptions["15594"]={cn:"特制的铲子，能让你挖进皇家螃蟹的花园。",en:"A special shovel that will let you dig holes all over the Royal Cwab\'s secret garden."};
descriptions["15596"]={cn:"暴躁的时候，对这个雕像发泄情绪。",en:"Something to look at when you\'re feeling crabby."};
descriptions["15599"]={cn:"这年头鹅毛笔太稀奇了，用鸵鸟剑写信才叫一个帅，灭哈哈哈！",en:"I write to you with a pistol in one hand and a sword in the other. The sword doubles up as a quill, mwahaha!"};
descriptions["15600"]={cn:"你只需要几件东西就可以补充你的鸟爪收集品了：一张网、一只巨大的捕鸟器以及几双能跑几千卡米的鞋子。",en:"You only need a few more things for your quest to complete your collection of claws: a huge net, an equally huge nail clipper, and some seven-kilokameter boots."};
descriptions["15601"]={cn:"你从鸵鸟的屁股上拔下了这根羽毛。你一定是个飞毛腿...或者是个鸵鸟狂热爱好者。",en:"The fact that you managed to pluck this feather out of a Strich\'s rump says something about you. Either you\'re an incredible sprinter... or you have an unnatural fetish for watching Striches sleep."};
descriptions["15602"]={cn:"精美的古代鸟嘴。看起来好像是从一只天界鸵鸟身上拔下来的。很有意思的发现...但是毫无用处。",en:"A fine, elegant, 10th-century beak. Looks like it was plucked from a Celestial Strich. An interesting find... but most probably worthless."};
descriptions["15603"]={cn:"15%云朵鸵鸟毛、8%脂肪以及77%未知原料...绝对是高级货。",en:"15% Cloudy Feathers, 8% fat and 77% unknown ingredients... This is definitely a quality ring."};
descriptions["15605"]={cn:"考虑到你始终佩戴着这对锋利、扎手的护肩，以后你上大巴之后那个恼人的女孩子再也不会坐在你身边了。",en:"Now that you have these sharp, scratchy epaulettes on all the time, that annoying girl you met on the bus will probably stop trying to sit next to you."};
descriptions["15606"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["15607"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["15608"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["15609"]={cn:"轻盈亮丽的护符，让你感觉飘飘然，就像暴发户买了飞机一样。",en:"Light and voluptuous, this amulet will make you feel like a million dollars whilst you\'re out courting con men and flying on the sordid wings of adventure."};
descriptions["15611"]={cn:"更轻便，更迅捷，更不要脸？",en:"You had always thought there\'d be more to your life than the whole \"bridle and groom\" story."};
descriptions["15612"]={cn:"有一吨羽毛这么重。",en:"As light as a ton of feathers."};
descriptions["15613"]={cn:"回家照镜子去，看看你都做了什么。",en:"Go home. Look in the mirror. Think about what you\'ve done."};
descriptions["15614"]={cn:"带着静电的小戒指，不停地发出呲呲呲的电流声！",en:"A little ring packed with static electricity. It just keeps going and going! Zzzzzrk!"};
descriptions["15616"]={cn:"睡前记得把鞋子脱下来，否则床单会被撕成破布。",en:"You should take these off before going to bed, unless you want to rip your sheets to shreds."};
descriptions["15617"]={cn:"富含琥珀，显示财富的所在。这只护符已经可以做展示品了！",en:"An rich amber amulet with beautiful hints of gold. This piece of jewelry is lovely enough to be in a haircare commercial!"};
descriptions["15619"]={cn:"没错，你头上顶了一只鸵鸟。怕什么？花了这么长时间拔上面的毛，戴在头上也没什么好害羞的。",en:"Yeah, you\'re wearing a Strich on your head, and what? You spent so long plucking it that it deserves pride of place in your outfit."};
descriptions["15620"]={cn:"谁想得到一只鸵鸟（即便是天界鸵鸟）会有如此漂亮的戒指？",en:"Who knew a Strich (even a Celestial one) could leave behind such a stunning ring?"};
descriptions["15621"]={cn:"到底要说几次你才明白？超级英雄都不穿披风，披风太危险了。可是你完全不是超级英雄的料，所以放心大胆地穿吧。",en:"How many times must you be told? Superheroes shouldn\'t wear capes; it\'s dangerous. Although you\'re nothing like a superhero, so maybe it\'s okay."};
descriptions["15622"]={cn:"看上去像普通的鸵鸟翅膀，实际上是神圣鸵鸟翅膀！不同凡响！",en:"These may look like ordinary Strich wings, but they\'re actually Divine Strich Wings! And that changes everything."};
descriptions["15623"]={cn:"草裙舞！是男人都喜欢！",en:"Crazy little party Strich, how I love her! Party party, always ready to dance."};
descriptions["15624"]={cn:"它们不会飞，不会战斗，甚至不会叫。但它们却是神。",en:"They can\'t fly, they can\'t fight, and they can\'t crow. But they are divine."};
descriptions["15625"]={cn:"挂在衣架上的时候，这东西看起来像个晕船的爱鱿。而穿在身上的时候，看上去...棒极了。起码奖励属性不错。",en:"On the hanger, this thing looks like a seasick Kralove; on your muscular chest, it will look like... Well, it\'ll look good. I mean, it\'ll look okay. The bonuses make it worthwhile."};
descriptions["15626"]={cn:"由鸵鸟羽毛制成，能适用于任何战场...起码可以用来当枕头。",en:"Crafted from heaps of Strich down and feathers, this shield will be a useful ally on the battlefield... Not least because it can also be used as a pillow when the fight is done and you need a rest."};
descriptions["15627"]={cn:"除了让你的手指更漂亮以外，还能自动除尘。",en:"As well as embellishing your finger, this little ring might help you with the dusting."};
descriptions["15634"]={cn:"每天清晨，一阵令人愉悦而放松的美妙气味从这件披风中散发出来，毫无疑问，这披风跟你的早餐特别配！",en:"Early in the morning, a lovely, relaxing scent is released from this cape. No doubt about it; this cape\'s breakfast\'s best friend!"};
descriptions["15711"]={cn:"这份文件授予你\"970年度阿玛克纳最佳\"称号。蕾顿·麦克艾伦为你骄傲！",en:"This document enables you to claim the title of Miss or Mister Amakna 970. Yungold McFroggileg would be so proud of you!"};
descriptions["15712"]={cn:"这份文件授予你\"970年度邦塔最佳\"称号。蕾顿·麦克艾伦为你骄傲！",en:"This document enables you to claim the title of Miss or Mister Bonta 970. Yungold McFroggileg would be so proud of you!"};
descriptions["15713"]={cn:"这份文件授予你\"970年度布拉克玛最佳\"称号。蕾顿·麦克艾伦为你骄傲！",en:"This document enables you to claim the title of Miss or Mister Brakmar 970. Yungold McFroggileg would be so proud of you!"};
descriptions["15714"]={cn:"这份文件授予你\"970年度萨弗基亚最佳\"称号。蕾顿·麦克艾伦为你骄傲！",en:"This document enables you to claim the title of Miss or Mister Sufokia 970. Yungold McFroggileg would be so proud of you!"};
descriptions["15715"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few drops should suffice."};
descriptions["15733"]={cn:"用于挖掘地底，找出藏在你家地下的小动物。现在你知道你的玩具茶杯去哪儿了吧！",en:"You can use this shield to dig into the ground and discover the family of tiny people living under your house. So that\'s where all your toy teacups went!"};
descriptions["15734"]={cn:"把你的手指塞进去！",en:"Put your finger in the hole!"};
descriptions["15735"]={cn:"每天晚上钻地前都要对着地面闻30秒。这样你有充分的时间穿上睡衣，梳梳头发，然后再尖叫着冲出去喊救命。",en:"This amulet starts snuffling 30 seconds before night-time fire drills, which should give you time to put on your pajama bottoms and comb your hair before going outside."};
descriptions["15736"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["15738"]={cn:"好像被扔在了创生能量之中。否则怎么会如此闪亮？",en:"This strange hat appears to have been dipped in a Wakfu Source. How else could it have gotten so shiny?"};
descriptions["15739"]={cn:"盾的背面刻着一行字，仍然依稀可辨：\n纪念我收过的好人卡...约...。",en:"Engraved on the back of this extraordinary shield, you can still make out parts of a tiny inscription: \"In memory of a love that wasn\'t to be... M... P.\""};
descriptions["15740"]={cn:"用这把充满创生能量的宝剑，你将变成世上最强的剑客！",en:"With this Wakfu-filled blade, you\'re the greatest swordsman that ever lived!"};
descriptions["15741"]={cn:"宠物染料可以于宠物设定介面中更改。此物品已无用处，可以将其分解掉。",en:"Pet colorings can be changed in the pet settings interface. This item is obsolete; you can recycle it."};
descriptions["15746"]={cn:"无比白净的豆芙...一尘不染！",en:"A Tofu that\'s whiter than white - you won\'t get any dirt on this one!"};
descriptions["15768"]={cn:"柔软蓬松的公仔，大家都想要！",en:"This downy fella is so cute that anyone would want him as a best friend!"};
descriptions["15769"]={cn:"情圣你好！为了奖励你在爱情表白上的功力和努力，我们授予你这个称号。",en:"You silver-quilled devil! You\'ve been awarded this title for writing the most beautiful declaration of love in your category."};
descriptions["15770"]={cn:"纪念你曾经拔光天界鸵鸟的羽毛。",en:"Look, Harry! It\'s the golden Strich!"};
descriptions["15771"]={cn:"快看，哈瑞！一只黄金鸵鸟！",en:"Look, Harry! It\'s the golden Strich!"};
descriptions["15772"]={cn:"至少这只不会在你的庇护袋里挖个洞！",en:"At least you can trust this one not to dig holes in your Haven Bag!"};
descriptions["15774"]={cn:"多用途测试",en:"Various Tang Use Test"};
descriptions["15775"]={cn:"没必要放在手里翻来覆去，它不会叫唤。",en:"Don\'t turn it upside down, it won\'t moo."};
descriptions["15788"]={cn:"苟余爱吃鱼，更爱宝藏。",en:"Hake loves fish, obviously, but the one thing he loves even more than fish is his Krosmaster collection... Handmade... out of seashells."};
descriptions["15789"]={cn:"就算没有肉体，生活还是要继续。",en:"Bawbossi, Bawbossa, life goes on, bra, la la how the life goes on."};
descriptions["15790"]={cn:"一日三餐他都吃豌豆汤，你可以想象他放屁的气味...",en:"For breakfast, he has pea green soup. For dinner, he has pea green soup. And when he springs a leak, all he can do is..."};
descriptions["15791"]={cn:"拉希把一辈子都赌在了这个指环上。",en:"You can bet your life that this ring\'ll come in handy. Cap\'n Craps did..."};
descriptions["15792"]={cn:"奥维船长出海，葬身鱼腹...*海上联播*",en:"He set out for a simple sail, but wound up inside a whale, Ohhh, Cap\'n Haba! The swirling eddies of Zinit destroyed the magical dream, ohhh...! *guitar solo*"};
descriptions["15793"]={cn:"其实是个小酒瓶，柯格船长的最爱。",en:"This amulet is equipped with a tiny flask of WD-For-Thee, Cap\'n Krik\'s favorite tipple when he\'s out on the open seas."};
descriptions["15794"]={cn:"传说这枚护符是由柯龙大师亲自交给阿玛克纳船长的。",en:"Legend has it that Cap\'n Amakna received this amulet after a private training session with Master Kano."};
descriptions["15795"]={cn:"有一次骸骨船长在巴格缇酒馆喝醉了。他对着酒保大喊“知道我为什么孤零零的么？我连喝酒的朋友都没有！”话音刚落，他断了一根骨头...",en:"This one time, when Cap\'n Chafer was at the Bagrutte Inn, he called out: \"Barkeep! Know why I\'m here alone? I had no body to invite!\" KLAK KLAK KLAK!!!"};
descriptions["15796"]={cn:"米莫船长早年丧母。他参加学校野营的时候被绑架，然后被关在了一个玻璃监狱里...眼泪流下来了...",en:"Cap\'n Nebo didn\'t have an easy childhood... He lost his mother very early on, was kidnapped during a school field trip, and was locked up in a glass prison."};
descriptions["15797"]={cn:"曾经属于一个植物术士。我说，除了萨迪达人谁还会想到用树皮和草绳编腰带？",en:"This belt used to belong to a Sadida. I mean, who else would wear a belt lined with Reinette fur on the inside and Strichon down on the outside?"};
descriptions["15798"]={cn:"柔顺丝滑的传统腰带，足够让你在有氧操课程上引人注目。",en:"Smooth, suave and traditional, this belt is all you need to groove to the vibe and be stylish all aerobics class long. Probably."};
descriptions["15799"]={cn:"毛网船长十分在意自己的发型；他相信这场战斗将事关十二世界的存亡。",en:"Captain Hairnet was always interested in promoting clean hair; he believed that this fight was the key to controlling the chaos and disorder that plagued the waters of the World of Twelve."};
descriptions["15800"]={cn:"船长只留下了这双靴子。终有一天，我将为船长复仇，让背叛者血债血偿。",en:"This is all that remains of the illustrious Cap\'n Dark Hurl. Fret not, my Captain, for one day I shall take vengeance for your death and the rebel Nations will sink at my feet."};
descriptions["15801"]={cn:"船长只留下了这双靴子。终有一天，我将平息流言，让公平与正义再次闪耀。",en:"This is all that remains of the illustrious Cap\'n Pavement. Fret not, my Captain, for one day I shall find the one who spoke evil words about you, and order and justice will be afloat once more."};
descriptions["15802"]={cn:"船长只留下了这双靴子。终有一天，我将查明船长死因，让真相大白于天下。",en:"This is all that remains of the illustrious Cap\'n LeChouque. Fret not, my Captain, for one day I shall shine light upon your death and the truth will explode in the faces of the ignorant masses."};
descriptions["15803"]={cn:"船长只留下了这双靴子。终有一天，我将解开所有秘密，让布拉克玛人人景仰我。",en:"This is all that remains of the illustrious Captain Ardier. Fret not, my Captain, for one day I shall pierce the mystery that links the two of us, and become so dastardly that Brakmar will be proud of me."};
descriptions["15804"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the frozen substance contained in this flask! A few drops should suffice."};
descriptions["15805"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the powdery substance contained in this flask! A few flakes should suffice."};
descriptions["15806"]={cn:"只是一点冰渣...",en:"It is not actually a seed, but a little icicle... But if you use it correctly, it\'ll sprout many terrible things!"};
descriptions["15807"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few drops should suffice."};
descriptions["15812"]={cn:"能提供少量经验加成。",en:"This candy will give you a little experience bonus."};
descriptions["15813"]={cn:"提高你的经验奖励。",en:"This candy will give you a comfortable experience bonus."};
descriptions["15814"]={cn:"大幅提高你找到宝藏的概率。",en:"This candy will greatly improve your chances of finding neat stuff."};
descriptions["15815"]={cn:"能小幅度提高找到宝物的几率。",en:"This candy will slightly improve your chances of finding items."};
descriptions["15816"]={cn:"独特的徽章，戴起来之后化身萨满。",en:"Just remember: be yourselves!"};
descriptions["15818"]={cn:"生于寒冰之地的一种小喵，为了抵御寒冷长着一身纯净无暇的白毛，这也为它常年在冰原上活动提供了完美的保护色。据说为了对付当地大肆繁殖的疯兔，早在千年之前人们就已经把喵喵引入到了阿玛克纳。现在它们的后代对陆地和海洋已经完全没有概念了。",en:"This little Bow Meow was born on Frigost, and its coat evolved to its immaculate ice-blue hue to better withstand the cold. This attribute also serves as camouflage amidst the ice. The Bow Meow may have been imported to Amakna during the Dofus Age to fight against the proliferation of Wabbits, but this sub-species seems never to have known terra firma!"};
descriptions["15819"]={cn:"小而强大。虽然已经生锈，却依然能制造巨大的嘈杂声。",en:"It may be small, but it makes a tremendous racket on account of its poorly lubricated machinery!"};
descriptions["15820"]={cn:"带它出门你就准备好被它牵着团团转吧，估计最后还得摔个狗吃屎！",en:"You\'ll be running round like a headless chicken after this little pest. He\'ll make you bite the dust in the end!"};
descriptions["15823"]={cn:"至少比玻璃眼睛漂亮！",en:"It\'s just cooler than a glass eye!"};
descriptions["15824"]={cn:"一个能够提醒你时间为何物的纪念品！",en:"A souvenir to remind you what time it is!"};
descriptions["15827"]={cn:"冰冻刺骨！",en:"This thing is frozen to the... bone!"};
descriptions["15829"]={cn:"狭义上的冰棍。即：冰棍吃完了，剩下的那根棍。",en:"The only thing left from this ice lolly is the stick."};
descriptions["15830"]={cn:"你认为是谁在因为内心的孤寂而哭啊，哭啊，哭...？",en:"Who\'d have thought that this lovely statue cries, cries, cries in its lonely heart?"};
descriptions["15831"]={cn:"如果你碰巧有一把勺子，那就快挖一勺！",en:"If only you had a tiny plastic spoon, you\'d tuck right in!"};
descriptions["15832"]={cn:"一个能够提醒你时间为何物的纪念品！",en:"Finally, something that will go with your Wawa pedal!"};
descriptions["15833"]={cn:"她是真的有一双美丽的...大雪球！",en:"She really does have a nice pair of snowballs!"};
descriptions["15834"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种叮当作响的物质收集到小瓶子里。只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An meticulous trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the clanky screws and bolts contained in this flask! A few gears should suffice."};
descriptions["15835"]={cn:"喂，你螺丝松了！",en:"Have you got a screw loose?"};
descriptions["15837"]={cn:"形似一把小发条，用于重启生锈的机械。",en:"This little item in the shape of a tiny key serves to reactivate jammed mechanisms."};
descriptions["15838"]={cn:"随时确保绳子已经绑牢！",en:"No need to make a mountain out of a molehill; just make sure you\'re always properly equipped!"};
descriptions["15839"]={cn:"钥匙结冰了还能塞得进钥匙孔吗？",en:"Will it still fit into a keyhole even though it\'s covered in ice?"};
descriptions["15840"]={cn:"需要新鲜空气？\n想也别想！",en:"Need to get some air?\nYou\'re not allowed out without a scarf, now!"};
descriptions["15843"]={cn:"一颗融化的心，就像你身体里的那颗一样！",en:"A little melting heart, crunchy as your heart\'s desire!"};
descriptions["15844"]={cn:"让拥有者不畏严寒，不畏攻击。",en:"This ice can make anything that touches it immune to cold and highly resistant to attack."};
descriptions["15845"]={cn:"谁能想得到有一天你也用得到冰冻的猪鬃？",en:"Who would have thought that the frozen pelt of a big hairy pig might be of interest to you one day?"};
descriptions["15846"]={cn:"厚实坚韧，隔离了所有寒气。",en:"This leather is so thick, it\'s impossible for the cold to get through. But that doesn\'t mean that it\'s not cold to the touch. Brrr!"};
descriptions["15847"]={cn:"离开饭冰冰！离远点！不许跟我抢皮！",en:"Leave Brrrbley alone!\nRight\nnow!\nI mean it!"};
descriptions["15848"]={cn:"绒毛团就长这样！",en:"So that\'s what a white featherweight hairball looks like!"};
descriptions["15849"]={cn:"即便它看起来像狗，也是会用牙齿咬人的！",en:"He may be a YeCh\'Ti, but he\'s not slow to show his fangs!"};
descriptions["15850"]={cn:"感谢忠实的你订阅一年的游戏时间，请收下这一特殊称号兹以奖励！",en:"A special title to thank you for your loyalty and your one-year subscription at the game\'s launch!"};
descriptions["15851"]={cn:"即便仅仅是挂在楼下衣帽架上，依然让你觉得温暖舒适。",en:"A cloak that\'ll keep you warm, even when it\'s hanging on the coat rack downstairs."};
descriptions["15852"]={cn:"穿上它，背后暗箭将毫无用处。",en:"With this cape on, arrows in the back will bounce straight off again."};
descriptions["15853"]={cn:"这么小个酒瓶，里面没多少酒，还都结冰了。喝不了，干瞪眼！",en:"The small amount of rum contained in this flask is completely frozen. What a let-down!"};
descriptions["15854"]={cn:"你可以用这件装备来短暂的探索尼莱扎的地窖，但是你得时刻注意过滤网的状态。",en:"You can use this equipment to explore Nileza\'s Vault for a short period of time, but keep an eye on the filter."};
descriptions["15855"]={cn:"这个沙漏让你可以使用神之界的时空裂痕。",en:"This sandglass allows you to use the time rifts in Ingloriom\'s temple."};
descriptions["15856"]={cn:"北地骸骨喝过小瓶朗姆酒所留下的，小心处置！",en:"This bottle was concocted from the remains of the Flasks of Rum gleaned from the Northern Chafers. Watch out, it will sure tickle your gums!"};
descriptions["15857"]={cn:"解开蒸汽之锁的钥匙。",en:"The key to the Lock of Steam, surprisingly enough."};
descriptions["15858"]={cn:"这样一把不起眼的钥匙居然能打开熔岩锁！",en:"The key to the Lock of Magma, surprisingly enough."};
descriptions["15859"]={cn:"解开生命之锁的钥匙。",en:"The key to the Lock of Life, surprisingly enough."};
descriptions["15860"]={cn:"解开死亡之锁的钥匙。",en:"The key to the Lock of Death, surprisingly enough."};
descriptions["15861"]={cn:"解开超凡秘密的钥匙。",en:"The key to the Lock of Immortality, surprisingly enough."};
descriptions["15862"]={cn:"矿石碎片。",en:"Small splinters of Taroudium ore."};
descriptions["15863"]={cn:"不用肝脑涂地，就可以染上胆汁黄。",en:"The easiest way to get yellow without ruining your liver."};
descriptions["15864"]={cn:"用于容纳各种矿物资源！\n只能存放与采矿有关的物品和资源。",en:"This box is just the place for your miner resources!\nIt can only contain items and resources linked to the miner profession."};
