descriptions["15927"]={cn:"哇哦，踮起脚来看！",en:"This will keep your friends on their toes all night long!"};
descriptions["15928"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["15929"]={cn:"混到队伍里就看不出来啦。",en:"This costume will permit you to blend into the crowd without attracting any suspicious looks."};
descriptions["15930"]={cn:"梦想成真了？真不敢相信！\n你毫无疑问是巡回武场的最强者，所以你有理由相信！",en:"You\'re not exactly a dream come true.\nBut you are my Champion of Mobile Arenas, and that\'ll have to do!"};
descriptions["15931"]={cn:"这块振动的铁矿是某件武器的碎片。\n仔细检查，看看能发现什么。\n\n该物品将触发一个任务。",en:"This vibrant piece of metal appears to be part of a weapon. Examine it more closely to determine what it could be. You can launch a quest using this item."};
descriptions["15932"]={cn:"迪波尔神父的死亡证明！",en:"Here\'s proof that Father Deepboar is no longer of the living!"};
descriptions["15933"]={cn:"当人们变老的时候，都希望获得年轻人的尊重，抢装备的时候会优先考虑老人。\n神父除外，他实在太老了!",en:"When we reach a ripe old age, we have the right to demand respect from youths and even carry powerful weapons. Unfortunately for Father Deepboar, he\'s well beyond a ripe old age!"};
descriptions["15934"]={cn:"由塔罗迪姆矿石制成。",en:"The top part of a pickaxe made of Taroudium."};
descriptions["15935"]={cn:"这样子的彩蛋节礼物怎么样？你准备用它来做啥？我要坐在我的彩蛋上面一直到今年圣诞节。",en:"How\'s this for a Fleastermind prize? What are you doing with yours? I\'m going to sit on mine \'til Kwismas."};
descriptions["15936"]={cn:"守护者父母们通常用这样的床来考验儿媳的品格。姑娘们要睡在二十层绵球被褥的床上，然后猜猜被褥底下有没有藏着一颗豌豆。",en:"Feca parents use beds like these to test their potential daughters-in-law for suitability. The girl has to lie on the bed atop twenty Gobball fleeces and guess whether there\'s pee at the bottom or not."};
descriptions["15937"]={cn:"那天，爷爷把这块护盾送给了我，第二天我就被狼群袭击了。我真走运！",en:"This one time, Grandfather Feca left you this incredible iron shield. And ever since, you\'ve felt sooo powerful!"};
descriptions["15938"]={cn:"装着守护者的生活必需品：羊绒手套、羊绒短裤、羊绒帽子还有羊绒毛衫。好吧，都塞满了。",en:"Comes with all the Feca staples: woolly mittens, woolly underpants, woolly hats, and woolly jumpers. In fact, there\'s no room left inside. In fact, there\'s no room left inside."};
descriptions["15939"]={cn:"由正宗的羊毛制成。放心脱光衣服好了。邻居永远也别想看到你的裸体。",en:"Woven from genuine Gobball Wool. Your nudity is safe. The neighbors will never see your funny-shaped nipples."};
descriptions["15940"]={cn:"守护者的行军橱总是满满的，即便是刚买来的时候！",en:"This is a wardrobe. Really! \nYou can store things in it. Really!"};
descriptions["15941"]={cn:"由塔罗迪姆制成。",en:"A pickaxe made of Taroudium."};
descriptions["15942"]={cn:"这盏烛台含有布拉克玛火药岩，而且据说是从绵矛革的嘴里吐出来的。想想就带感啊！",en:"This lamp contains Brakmarian lava and is so horrifically unstable that people say it comes from the mouth of the untamable Magmog. Imagine that!"};
descriptions["15943"]={cn:"好好牧羊，羊也会好好牧你的。",en:"Take care of your staff, and your staff will take care of you."};
descriptions["15944"]={cn:"大桌子上摆满小瓶子，守护者就喜欢这样。只是这些饮料尝起来一股人工合成的味道。",en:"Smells like slobber and old sausages."};
descriptions["15945"]={cn:"玩家排排坐挨个敲钉子，敲最后一枚钉子的罚说真心话。",en:"Each player takes a hammer and waits for his or her turn to hammer one, two, or three nails into the table. Whoever hammers in the last nail loses."};
descriptions["15946"]={cn:"好有个性的一种植物。时间长了，它不会枯萎而是...生锈。",en:"This plant\'s most characteristic feature is that, when it dies, it rusts instead of wilting."};
descriptions["15947"]={cn:"寒冰咕哩踏雪无痕的秘诀就是这双靴子...",en:"The Brrrblis trample the ice as they stampede, but the island\'s temperature instantly freezes the water after they have passed, creating pretty white ripples."};
descriptions["15948"]={cn:"只要亮出爪子，就能赶走敌人。",en:"Just show a white paw as proof of good faith to enter the fold!"};
descriptions["15949"]={cn:"源于寒冰夫人的第一次死灵法术实验。品质优良，骸骨军团成员每人一双。",en:"These boots were the result of Freezz\'s very first Neoromantic Smithmagic experiments. They were so successful that all the Chafers in her army were duly equipped."};
descriptions["15950"]={cn:"保护你的正面和背面免受严寒，其他部位受到伤害没人管得着...",en:"This breastplate shields your front and behind, so feel free to take some hits for the others!"};
descriptions["15951"]={cn:"极地碎石者全身被厚实坚硬的冰层覆盖，坚不可摧。",en:"Polar Cracklers are covered in thick, tough ice that is practically unbreakable!"};
descriptions["15952"]={cn:"源于寒冰夫人的第一次死灵法术实验。品质优良，骸骨军团成员人手一件。",en:"This breastplate was the result of Freezz\'s very first Neoromantic Smithmagic experiments. It was so successful that all the Chafers in her army were duly equipped."};
descriptions["15953"]={cn:"没有什么东西可以刺进这件披风。坚不可摧。",en:"Its purpose is simple: nothing can penetrate it. It would appear to work perfectly."};
descriptions["15954"]={cn:"温暖舒适，柔软顺滑。雨天防雨，雪天防滑。",en:"Warm, soft and hairy, what could be better when it\'s raining cats and dogs?"};
descriptions["15955"]={cn:"这么冷的天气带着这条腰带没事吗？你可没有寒冰咕哩那么厚的脂肪！",en:"It\'s not a good idea to tighten your belt in such freezing conditions! Better go out on a full stomach: after all, you\'re not endowed with an extra layer of fat like a Brrrbli."};
descriptions["15956"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["15957"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["15958"]={cn:"小巧可爱，力量强大。",en:"Tiny, sweet, gentle and cool. Tough, white, and oh so powerful!"};
descriptions["15959"]={cn:"戴着这枚戒指的时候，想不冻僵手指也难。",en:"It\'s difficult for your fingers not to freeze off while wearing this ring."};
descriptions["15960"]={cn:"源于寒冰夫人的第一次死灵法术实验。品质优良，骸骨军团成员人手一个。",en:"This ring was the result of Freezz\'s very first Neoromantic Smithmagic experiments. It was so successful that all the Chafers in her army were duly equipped."};
descriptions["15961"]={cn:"从远处看和寒冰奇境的野兽一模一样。",en:"From afar, you could almost be mistaken for a Boohemoth lost in the icy wasteland of Frigost!"};
descriptions["15962"]={cn:"极地碎石者是寒冰夫人的实验产物。可惜实验失败了，剩下的极地碎石者在大陆上游荡，威胁着冒险者。",en:"The Polar Cracklers are the result of several experiments carried out by Missiz Freezz. These monsters were one of her failures, so why oh why didn\'t she destroy them rather than letting them live on to threaten adventurers?"};
descriptions["15963"]={cn:"腰带表面覆盖这一层薄薄的冰霜。任何有自尊的冒险者都应该在寒冰奇境试穿这条腰带一星期！",en:"The frost that covers this belt lends it a certain refinement. Any self-respecting adventurer owes it to himself to wear it at least once a week when on Frigost Island!"};
descriptions["15964"]={cn:"狩猎的象征。",en:"One of the most popular hunting trophies with our friends the hunters."};
descriptions["15965"]={cn:"由塔罗迪姆矿石制成，决定了极地碎石者的硬度。",en:"This amulet is studded with Taroudium chips, which assure the legendary resistance of the Polar Cracklers."};
descriptions["15966"]={cn:"源于寒冰夫人的第一次死灵法术实验。品质优良，骸骨军团成员人手一条。",en:"This amulet was the result of Freezz\'s very first Neoromantic Smithmagic experiments. It was so successful that all the Chafers in her army were duly equipped."};
descriptions["15967"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["15968"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["15969"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["15970"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["15971"]={cn:"根据标准模式设计，无论你怎么穿，都能完美匹配你的身材。",en:"Designed according to a standard model, this breastplate serves its purpose regardless of which way round you wear it."};
descriptions["15972"]={cn:"这件头盔唯一的缺点是太大，会导致视野受阻。",en:"The reduced field of vision appears to be the only drawback of this unbelievably tough helmet."};
descriptions["15973"]={cn:"完美契合肩膀形状，能使行动更加流畅。",en:"These epaulettes fit the shoulder joint to perfection, facilitating extremely rapid movements."};
descriptions["15974"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["15975"]={cn:"饭冰冰最爱的指环，但愿她还带得上。",en:"This ring is the centerpiece of Brrrbley Spears\'s collection and would be worth its weight in gold if only the market wasn\'t frozen."};
descriptions["15976"]={cn:"轻若无物。即便行走在冰上也不会留下丝毫脚印。",en:"Very light, these boots are made for walking on the thinnest parts of the ice without leaving the slightest trace of a footfall!"};
descriptions["15977"]={cn:"饭冰冰时常在寒冰大陆上，眺望子嗣们到处乱窜...",en:"In the midst of the icicles rearing up all over the Ice Floe, Brrrbley Spears watches over her children."};
descriptions["15978"]={cn:"由坚硬的皮革制成。穿上之后，你觉得寒冷刺骨。",en:"This cloak couldn\'t be less toxic: it\'s made of dry old leather, frozen by the cold!"};
descriptions["15979"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["15980"]={cn:"冰冻棒棒糖是寒冰夫人最棒的实验品。可以唤醒死者！\n早上来一根冰冻棒棒糖可以使处于恢复期的你迅速恢复。",en:"Freezepop - the coolest ice confection around, from Missiz Freezz!\nIt\'ll wake the dead!\nA Freezepop in the morning to dispel De Darm and all those nasty effects associated with death!"};
descriptions["15982"]={cn:"让你转生之后变得更大...更好...更强...",en:"The only scroll you need to come back bigger... better... stronger..."};
descriptions["15983"]={cn:"一枚漂亮的冰卡玛！别藏在兜里太久了哦，与其等它化掉不如先去花掉！",en:"A magnificent ice kama! Don\'t keep it inside in the warmth too long or you might find yourself with nothing but a wet patch!"};
descriptions["15984"]={cn:"一根棒棒糖...",en:"A key in the shape of an iced candy..."};
descriptions["15985"]={cn:"这块冰闪烁着奇怪的光芒。仔细检查这块冰，看看里面有什么。\n\n该物品将触发一个任务。",en:"This fragment of ice gleams in a strange way. Examine it more closely to determine what it could be. \nYou can launch a quest using this item."};
descriptions["15986"]={cn:"一根经历了时间磨砺和骸骨噬咬的棒棒糖。",en:"An Freezepop weathered by time and marked by Chafer teeth."};
descriptions["15987"]={cn:"曾经属于欧格梅泽的靴子，现在已经破烂不堪。也许技艺高超的鞋匠能修好。",en:"These worn-out boots once belonged to Hogmeiser. They are so worn they are crippling. With a bit of luck, a skilled shoemaker should be able to repair them."};
descriptions["15988"]={cn:"鲁图图有另外一个响亮的名字：波维瑟。即便上了年纪，这名匠人依然富有创造力。",en:"This belt bears the ridiculous name of its creator, Luthuthu, a shoemaker much less well known than Bowisse, yet still very creative despite his advanced age."};
descriptions["15989"]={cn:"由纯净塔罗迪姆矿石制成，能让寒冰夫人为之颤抖。",en:"Made from Pure Taroudium, this pickaxe is sure to send a shudder through Missiz Freezz\'s heart."};
descriptions["15990"]={cn:"来自上古时代，充满粘性的液体。",en:"A sticky liquid that seems to come from another age."};
descriptions["15992"]={cn:"教会你用一种神秘的矿石制造头盔。",en:"A recipe explaining how to craft a helmet from an unusual mineral!"};
descriptions["15993"]={cn:"用来打开塔顶的密室。",en:"To unlock the inner sanctum at the top of the Frozen Tower."};
descriptions["15994"]={cn:"可控召唤物测试",en:"Controllable Summons Test"};
descriptions["15997"]={cn:"你曾经让皇家布丁跪地痛哭求饶。",en:"A battle trophy to remind you of your victory in the dungeon."};
descriptions["15998"]={cn:"这个奖章是授予有功的贵族以及贵妇，这份礼物是国家以其为荣以其为傲的标志...呃？噢...你又消失了。",en:"This title is reserved for deserving noblemen and -women. It is with great pleasure and pride that the court presents... Huh? Oh... You\'ve disappeared again."};
descriptions["15999"]={cn:"这个头衔是为高贵的男士和女士们准备的。现在本庭带着骄傲和荣耀将头衔授予...呃？哦...人又不见了。",en:"This title is reserved for deserving noblemen and -women. It is with great pleasure and pride that the court presents... Huh? Oh... You\'ve disappeared again."};
descriptions["16000"]={cn:"这个头衔是为高贵的男士和女士们准备的。现在本庭带着骄傲和荣耀将头衔授予...呃？哦...人又不见了。",en:"This title is reserved for deserving noblemen and -women. It is with great pleasure and pride that the court presents... Huh? Oh... You\'ve disappeared again."};
descriptions["16001"]={cn:"这个头衔是为高贵的男士和女士们准备的。现在本庭带着骄傲和荣耀将头衔授予...呃？哦...人又不见了。",en:"This title is reserved for deserving noblemen and -women. It is with great pleasure and pride that the court presents... Huh? Oh... You\'ve disappeared again."};
descriptions["16002"]={cn:"这个头衔是为高贵的男士和女士们准备的。现在本庭带着骄傲和荣耀将头衔授予...呃？哦...人又不见了。",en:"This title is reserved for deserving noblemen and -women. It is with great pleasure and pride that the court presents... Huh? Oh... You\'ve disappeared again."};
descriptions["16007"]={cn:"保暖性能极好，即便面临暴风雪也无所谓畏惧。",en:"These shoulder pads are incredibly frost-resistant and are very useful when plunging headlong into a blizzard, as you do."};
descriptions["16008"]={cn:"轻轻一戳就能刺穿冰面！",en:"The slightest stroke of this sword is enough to break the ice!"};
descriptions["16009"]={cn:"深处寒冰奇境，你得穿得暖些，特别是脑袋。",en:"You\'ve got to wrap up warmly on Frigost Island, especially your head. You wouldn\'t want to end up with Iop brain-freeze, would you?"};
descriptions["16010"]={cn:"用来碎冰的最好选择。只是实在太冻手了...",en:"This hammer would be the ultimate ice-breaker, if it weren\'t so cold to handle."};
descriptions["16011"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["16012"]={cn:"饭冰冰是真正的领导者，深受寒冰咕哩家族尊敬。这条坠饰彰显寒冰咕哩家族所有的敬意。",en:"Brrrbley Spears is a true leader; the Brrrblis hold her in profound esteem! This amulet reflects all the love they have for their mistress."};
descriptions["16013"]={cn:"饭冰冰随身携带的匕首，",en:"This dagger is as lethal as the ice floe that Brrrbley Spears has chosen to make her home!"};
descriptions["16014"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["16015"]={cn:"不要被外表欺骗了。吉狼狼根本没穿过肩甲。",en:"Don\'t be fooled by their appearance; these epaulettes definitely come from the YeCh\'Ti\'Wawa. Even though they could cover his entire body if he ever wore them."};
descriptions["16016"]={cn:"感受吉狼狼的愤怒吧。唉？对了，你打疫苗了没？",en:"The YeCh\'Ti\'Wawa\'s rabid rage is concentrated in this breastplate. If drool starts dripping from the corners of your mouth, then it\'s already too late."};
descriptions["16018"]={cn:"曾经是吉狼狼的项圈...",en:"This amulet could be used as a belt by the YeCh\'Ti\'Wawa, which is no reason to use it to tie up weaklings."};
descriptions["16019"]={cn:"只是腰带，不是项圈！",en:"This belt can be used as a leash, which is no reason to use it as a necklace."};
descriptions["16022"]={cn:"这是一位已故之人留下的。说不定是你的朋友...",en:"These are the remains of a deceased person. Maybe one of your old friends..."};
descriptions["16025"]={cn:"可以用来生火，只需要拿火柴在坠饰上擦一擦。",en:"This amulet can be used to light a fire. Just scrape a small Taroudium-coated match along the pendant."};
descriptions["16026"]={cn:"这块护盾的坚硬程度和温度成反比。温度越低，越是坚硬。",en:"This shield\'s toughness is inversely proportional to the temperature outside. The colder it gets, the tougher it becomes."};
descriptions["16027"]={cn:"靴子留下的脚印让人想起有翅膀的生物。",en:"The footprints left by these boots call to mind the traces left by a winged creature."};
descriptions["16028"]={cn:"胆小鬼别戴。",en:"If you get cold feet, just give your friend a ring."};
descriptions["16029"]={cn:"毛茸茸的披风，穿上后不惧寒冷，就是有点痒...",en:"It\'s the most powerful cloak in the nation, and you\'re giving it a piggyback. A classic example of \'I scratch your back, you scratch mine.\'"};
descriptions["16030"]={cn:"两面都有锯齿。必要的时候，完全可以用作锯子。",en:"This weapon does just as much damage on the way back as it does on the way there. It can even be used as a saw when necessary."};
descriptions["16031"]={cn:"美妙的冬季果实。",en:"These ice pines are wondrous winter fruits."};
descriptions["16032"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["16033"]={cn:"胸甲是哈根达兹套装中最闪亮的部件，作为收藏品相当漂亮。",en:"Armor is Hagen Daz\'s shiny centerpiece, and it\'s so powerful that it can\'t help but find a place in your collection."};
descriptions["16034"]={cn:"塔罗迪姆矿含量相当高，极易吸引劫匪！",en:"This amulet is so high in Taroudium that it may cause unwanted side effects!"};
descriptions["16035"]={cn:"哈根·达兹曾经是个极地碎石者。他吞下了太多塔罗迪姆矿石，变异成了可怕的怪物！",en:"Hagen Daz was a Polar Crackler like the others, until the day he swallowed so much Taroudium for breakfast that he mutated into a terrifying monster!"};
descriptions["16036"]={cn:"穿上肩甲，与寒冰奇境融为一体！",en:"Prepare to assume the appearance of an icy colossus and be at one with the Frigostian environment!"};
descriptions["16037"]={cn:"与浮冰大陆融为一体。",en:"This cloak melts into the surrounding ice floe."};
descriptions["16038"]={cn:"碎石指针一点，寒冰碎片飞溅！",en:"A little crunch of Crackercrumb will send ice sparks flying!"};
descriptions["16039"]={cn:"上面是矿石碎片，不是巧克力脆皮！",en:"Are those Taroudium Shards that you can glimpse through the layer of ice on these epaulettes?"};
descriptions["16040"]={cn:"有效抗寒，也许是因为塔罗迪姆矿石涂层的缘故。",en:"This ring helps to bear the cold, probably due to the subtle effect of its Taroudium content."};
descriptions["16041"]={cn:"这双靴子可以清除你屁股上所有的冰雪！",en:"These boots make it possible to dodge all the dangers of the Frigost pack ice without ending up on your butt!"};
descriptions["16042"]={cn:"由永恒冰晶制成。这对匕首足以刺穿任何材料。",en:"Made from Eternal Ice, these daggers can pierce any material except the Sun itself, or any science class replica of the Sun, or anything remotely warm, like a fresh loaf."};
descriptions["16043"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["16044"]={cn:"这枚戒指经由吉瓦祝福，寒冰夫人精心打造，是海尔伯格伯爵和寒冰夫人的定情信物。",en:"Tapping into the power granted by Jiva, Missiz Freezz created this ring as a symbol of her betrothal to Count Harebourg."};
descriptions["16045"]={cn:"相当惹眼的靴子，当年引得雪封村民疯抢。",en:"These boots allowed Missiz Freezz to convert a great deal of Frigost\'s population, who had initially been reluctant to serve her."};
descriptions["16046"]={cn:"含有一部分塔罗迪姆矿石粉末。也许这就是这件披风看起来优雅又飘逸的原因。",en:"The embroidery on this cloak is made from fine splinters of Taroudium. Quite how Missiz Freezz managed to make it so light and airy remains a mystery!"};
descriptions["16047"]={cn:"吉瓦送给寒冰夫人的礼物。从此以后，人们称寒冰夫人为“冰美人”！",en:"This belt was one of Jiva\'s gifts to Missiz Freezz. It earned her the nickname \"Buns of Ice\"!"};
descriptions["16048"]={cn:"运用远古炼金术知识，这件胸甲在穿戴者身上创造了一层厚厚的冰甲。",en:"Crafted using ancient smithmaging knowledge, this breastplate creates a thick layer of ice over its wearer that prevents him from healing properly."};
descriptions["16049"]={cn:"寒冰夫人热衷炼金术，她闲暇时经常制造一些坚盾送给心腹佩戴。",en:"Smithmagic was Freezz\'s favorite pastime. In her spare time, she created shields to equip some of her henchmen, making them even tougher."};
descriptions["16050"]={cn:"暖骨腰带是鞋匠克里姆的原创作品。每个人都有各自取暖的方式。",en:"The Warmabones Belt is an original design by Klime the Shoemaker. We all have our own little ways of keeping warm."};
descriptions["16051"]={cn:"鱼骨头用来当牙签也是不错的选择。",en:"The Ketcha Fish is famous for its sharp and tough bones. Perfect for using as toothpicks or piercing holes in cloaks."};
descriptions["16052"]={cn:"由塔罗迪姆矿石制成，寒冰夫人亲自向胸甲里吹了口气。现在你胸口爽极了！",en:"The breastplate was made out of Taroudium before Missiz Freezz added the finishing touches at her forge. It will let you keep your drinks cool between your shoulder blades."};
descriptions["16053"]={cn:"还是要记得保持头脑冷静！",en:"To keep a cool head!"};
descriptions["16054"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["16055"]={cn:"布满了螺栓螺帽。足够解决任何机械故障。",en:"Each of the two epaulettes carries a supply of nuts, bolts, and screws. Enough to take care of your followers in any circumstances imaginable."};
descriptions["16056"]={cn:"腰带上的每一个孔都插满了工具。没有任何一种机器能难倒你！",en:"Each one of this belt\'s slots is dedicated to a particular tool. With a waistline like that, no machine will be able to resist you!"};
descriptions["16057"]={cn:"人活着总要依靠别人帮忙的，戴上这个护符吧，让你看起来可怜巴巴的，好博得周围人们的同情心。",en:"You have to have some allies before you can support them. Luckily, this amulet seems to elicit the sympathies of all the creatures around."};
descriptions["16058"]={cn:"到处布满了修补的痕迹。他到底是怎么做到的？",en:"Repaired here and patched up there. How does he do it?"};
descriptions["16059"]={cn:"指环上有几个小小的插槽，可以在上面拧螺丝。",en:"This ring is equipped with small nozzles so that accessories can be attached to it."};
descriptions["16060"]={cn:"坚固的法杖头部是任何工匠的完美伴侣。自带33个连接器。",en:"This stick\'s transposable top makes it the perfect companion for any handyman. Comes with 33 different connectors."};
descriptions["16061"]={cn:"塞拉制作的腰带。能提升任何机械系统的功效。",en:"This drive belt, developed by Sylargh, multiplies the capabilities of any mechanical system."};
descriptions["16062"]={cn:"由最坚硬的械卡合金制成，每一箭都直击敌人要害。",en:"Made with the best Mecha alloy, this bow focuses on the pure essentials, making it lighter, finer, and more efficient."};
descriptions["16063"]={cn:"据塞拉本人描述，这件坠饰可以自我修正缺陷。",en:"According to Sylargh, the body is an imperfect machine, but this amulet can correct the defects."};
descriptions["16064"]={cn:"戴上手指的时候，只听咔嚓一声，然后全身充满了力量...",en:"A slight shock to the finger indicates that the ring is properly on. Then the power flows..."};
descriptions["16065"]={cn:"献给创生之力的信徒。",en:"For those who believe in the power of Wakfu."};
descriptions["16066"]={cn:"日记的一页，曾经属于货车的主人。",en:"An excerpt from a diary that must have belonged to the owner of the cart."};
descriptions["16068"]={cn:"穿越冰原的必备装备。",en:"Absolutely essential for little walks across the icy lands."};
descriptions["16069"]={cn:"现在你可以放心骑上寒冰咕哩了！",en:"Put your Lurgi-ridden days behind you with this nonchalant costume!"};
descriptions["16070"]={cn:"看起来有点毛糙，但是真的暖和！",en:"Whaddya know, an untreated Brrrbli Fur... It may be pretty rough but it\'s warmer than any other fur!"};
descriptions["16071"]={cn:"用史蒂芬·冰山的设备提取的样本。",en:"A piece of Pure Taroudium extracted using Styffen Chillberg\'s instruments."};
descriptions["16072"]={cn:"史蒂芬·冰山的财产。",en:"Property of Styffen Chillberg."};
descriptions["16073"]={cn:"上面的标签写着：史蒂芬·冰山所有物。除了本人以外，一切租用与销售行为将被严令禁止。",en:"The label reads: The invention and property of Styffen Chillberg.\nRental and sale by persons other than Mr. Chillberg are strictly prohibited."};
descriptions["16074"]={cn:"由塔罗迪姆矿石制成，硬度极高！",en:"This helmet was cast from Taroudium ore, so it\'s tremendously tough, especially in cold temperatures!"};
descriptions["16075"]={cn:"哈奇夫·塔伦 著",en:"By Hazieff Taroun"};
descriptions["16076"]={cn:"使劲抽，使劲！",en:"Want to find out how to apply a good lashing without hurting your fingers? Easy, just learn this scroll by heart!"};
descriptions["16077"]={cn:"哈奇夫·塔伦本人留下的笔记。",en:"A note left by Hazieff Taroun in person."};
descriptions["16079"]={cn:"由于法杖本身制作时使用了大量的雪原木以至于它看起来十分的光滑，然而它最大的特点是能够将敌人一分为二。",en:"This staff is made principally of Frozen Wood, which lends it a shiny and fragile appearance. One of its special features is its ability to split enemies in two!"};
descriptions["16080"]={cn:"不要让它勒的太紧，因为这个护符能够使任何触碰到它的东西瞬间冰封，你好，僵硬的脖子！",en:"Avoid tying this too tightly, as it instantly freezes anything it touches. Hello, stiff neck!"};
descriptions["16081"]={cn:"即便是寒冰咕哩面对这把法杖也要发疯抓狂！从此之后你能够击倒的小怪物就会不计其数！",en:"This wand will make all Brrrblis completely crazy about you!\nYou\'ll have little monsters coming at you by the bucket load!"};
descriptions["16082"]={cn:"要知道这张传说中的卧榻是使用饭冰冰自己的皮革制造而成！我不能保证它一定很舒服，当然别人怎么想我也不知道，不过有一点是确定的，只要你在上面睡上一晚后一定会觉得比前一天的力量更强大！",en:"This bed is made with several layers of leather from Brrrbley Spears herself! I wouldn\'t call it comfortable, but who knows, sleeping in it might actually make you stronger than yesterday!"};
descriptions["16083"]={cn:"虽然这把铲子能够像切黄油一样刺穿冰层，但是如果你不想掉进冰窟窿里就不要妄想去实践。",en:"This shovel has the ability to cut through ice like butter, but it\'s not recommended practice as you risk falling into an icy water hole!"};
descriptions["16084"]={cn:"这枚指环会让你由衷的置身于幸福之中，它能够净化佩戴者的灵魂使得佩戴者由内心深处迸发出纯净之火。",en:"This ring will make you melt with happiness. It affects the wearer in the depths of his soul to purify his heart of fiery flares!"};
descriptions["16085"]={cn:"用力挖！",en:"Dig in!"};
descriptions["16086"]={cn:"想要打破发霉的命运？玄冰披风是你最好的选择。",en:"Want to break free from the mold? You need the Great Ice Cape."};
descriptions["16087"]={cn:"哩冰冰是一头特立独行的寒冰咕哩。他的宁静生活被冰山来往的货车搅得一团糟。比起这些，他还很讨厌饭冰冰...",en:"Pumbrrr is one very solitary Brrrbli. Rejected by others for his spring flower fragrance, he wanders around Chillberg Island wrecking all before him. He also has a tendency to foil Chillberg\'s plans for expansion."};
descriptions["16088"]={cn:"厚实的披氅，深受寒冰奇境猎人赞赏。",en:"This thick coat won\'t let the cold through. It\'s prized by Frigostian hunters for exactly that reason."};
descriptions["16089"]={cn:"厚实的披风，再可怕的严寒也无法侵袭。深受冰山岛的猎人喜爱。",en:"This coat is very thick and the cold cannot penetrate it. It\'s prized by Frigostian hunters for exactly that reason."};
descriptions["16101"]={cn:"宠物染料可以于宠物设定介面中更改。此物品已无用处，可以将其分解掉。",en:"Pet colorings can be changed in the pet settings interface. This item is obsolete; you can recycle it."};
descriptions["16102"]={cn:"其实是兽医诊所钥匙。",en:"For little children who have not been good."};
descriptions["16104"]={cn:"这双靴子曾经属于克里姆，即便是在极端寒冷的环境下，穿着它依旧会感觉到舒适。",en:"These boots once belonged to Klime. They are resistant to extreme temperatures and provide an amazingly comfortable fit."};
descriptions["16105"]={cn:"书中自有真相。",en:"The truth is in the books."};
descriptions["16106"]={cn:"塔罗塔罗旺！这块皮革足以抵御任何低温。还等什么，赶快拥有它！",en:"Toura loura tarou lou rye yay! Now this leather is protected against negative temperatures!"};
descriptions["16107"]={cn:"这把铲子可以让你找出隐藏在阿斯图布，阿玛克纳，邦塔和萨弗基亚的五周年宝藏。",en:"This Shovel allows you to look for the Treasures hidden in Astrub, Amakna, Brakmar, Bonta and Sufokia, for the Wakfu Birthday (5 years)."};
descriptions["16108"]={cn:"雪地上的大脚，\n冰牙冻结了血液，\n独行巨兽来了。",en:"Hear his footfalls in the snow,\nHis fangs freeze the blood,\nLone Boohemoth is coming."};
descriptions["16109"]={cn:"属于雪封村的老医生。",en:"These gloves belonged to the old doctor in the Snowbound Village!"};
descriptions["16110"]={cn:"属于雪封村的前市长！",en:"This jacket belonged to the former deputy mayor of the Snowbound Village!"};
descriptions["16111"]={cn:"这块奖章曾经属于雪封村的坎蒂尔市长市长。",en:"This medal belonged to the former mayor of the Snowbound Village!"};
descriptions["16112"]={cn:"你看吧，没有任何东西能让你的秃头感到温暖！",en:"You see, nothing else could possibly keep your bald head warmer!"};
descriptions["16113"]={cn:"即便是锋利的北地狼人的獠牙也无法穿透这层护甲，这就能看出它是多么的坚韧。",en:"Even a Boohemoth couldn\'t pierce these with his fangs, which shows just how tough they are."};
descriptions["16114"]={cn:"事实已经证明它拥有极强的寒冰之力，能否将这种力量发挥出来则取决于你有多强的力量。",en:"The coolness of this collar has already been demonstrated. On the other hand, it is up to you to reveal all its power."};
descriptions["16115"]={cn:"狼有狼道。",en:"The Wawa in Wawa falls mainly on the Wawa. As people say around here."};
descriptions["16117"]={cn:"这把武器之所以强悍的原因就在于它的力量来源于无限的寒冰之力，传说它曾经击倒了名叫格兰·L的丑陋巨魔。",en:"This sword draws its power from the surrounding ice. Legend says that it killed Grand L, a misshapen Trool rapper."};
descriptions["16118"]={cn:"这件披风适用于所有喜欢独处时暴食甜点的美食家。",en:"This cloak is suitable for all great gourmets who like to be left alone whilst they guzzle down dessert."};
descriptions["16119"]={cn:"好顺，好顺，两副同花顺，胜利没跑的！",en:"You\'ll doubtless create stacks of two different colors, running from the highest card to the lowest... and win the game!"};
descriptions["16120"]={cn:"这件美丽的珠宝取材于被冰封的海水，如果你偶然尝到了它的味道，你一定会难过的跳脚！",en:"This beautiful jewelry is made from shimmering frozen seawater. If you happen to taste it inadvertently, you\'ll get an unpleasant surprise!"};
descriptions["16121"]={cn:"很久以前，雪封村经常遭受雪狼的侵袭。村民们即便死后变成了北地骸骨，也无法忘记这场战斗。他们再次对雪狼发动了攻击！",en:"In the past, the Snowbound Village was under constant attack by Snowfoux. The Northern Chafers, former villagers who are now dead, never forgot this affront, and, many years later, launched an attack on them!"};
descriptions["16122"]={cn:"拿雪狼当皮草之前，至少先要杀死它吧！",en:"Better not try wearing a Snowfoux\'s pelt before killing it!"};
descriptions["16123"]={cn:"北地骸骨老是穿着一身雪狼皮毛出来活动，迪波尔神父经常误以为是真的雪狼来了！",en:"The Northern Chafers got the better of the Snowfoux and proudly wear their skins. Father Deepboar is constantly mistaking them for actual Snowfoux!"};
descriptions["16124"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["16126"]={cn:"几乎是把万能钥匙！",en:"Always have a little key to hand!"};
descriptions["16127"]={cn:"某些场合，可以用来调试砰砰。",en:"A key that can even be used for some of Klap-Klap\'s settings."};
descriptions["16128"]={cn:"嗯...思考良久之后，你决定相信这柄钥匙能激活气艇的升降梯。",en:"Hmmmmmm... After much consideration, you believe this key may activate the zeppelin\'s elevator."};
descriptions["16129"]={cn:"最毒毁灭心！",en:"As cute as it is terrifying!"};
descriptions["16136"]={cn:"没有人知道这是什么东西...",en:"It is made ​​of a very strange sort of matter indeed... The good thing is that there\'s no danger of suffocating on it!"};
descriptions["16139"]={cn:"有了这柄指针，海尔伯格得以准确报时...",en:"Count Harebourg could use this to tell time with pinpoint accuracy."};
descriptions["16146"]={cn:"原本用于保护伯爵的大钟，对于防御攻击也十分有效。",en:"This was actually designed to bear Count Harebourg\'s Clock Hand, but it turned out to be extremely effective against attacks."};
descriptions["16147"]={cn:"精心提炼，外行会误以为是纯净塔罗迪姆矿石！",en:"So refined that you\'d think it was Pure Taroudium!"};
descriptions["16148"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["16149"]={cn:"这款戒指的设计相当不凡，你必须以顺时针的方向戴上它，也必须以逆时针的方向脱掉它。",en:"Fairly robust in its design, this ring should be put on the finger clockwise and removed by turning in a counter-clockwise direction."};
descriptions["16150"]={cn:"不要把这个大轮子当盘子来用，要知道它足以改变你的胃。",en:"Don\'t use this big wheel as a plate; it\'s enough to turn your stomach."};
descriptions["16151"]={cn:"既能当工具又能当武器，塞拉既用它来贯彻自己的权威也用来伐木。",en:"Half-tool, half-weapon, this ax allows Sylargh to instill authority when he\'s not sawing planks for odd jobs."};
descriptions["16152"]={cn:"这个胸甲看起来只有轻薄一片，但是它的抵抗力却超乎你的想象之外。",en:"This breastplate appears to have been cast in a single piece. It protects against the often violent discharges that arise from metalwork."};
descriptions["16158"]={cn:"由史蒂芬·冰山绘制的海图，标明了海盗营地的位置。一定是这些坏蛋偷走了货物。",en:"This map drawn by Chillberg indicates the location of the pirates\' camp. Those no-good barbarians were behind the theft of his cargo of Taroudium."};
descriptions["16159"]={cn:"历尽艰险的你赢得的奖励。你可以用这枚奖章兑换装备。",en:"You can trade in this hard-won token for pieces of equipment."};
descriptions["16160"]={cn:"粘稠、腥臭的血液。不是给人用的消耗品，它反而会“消耗”人...",en:"The stickiest, stinkiest blood you\'ve ever seen. Not recommended for human consumption."};
