descriptions["16489"]={cn:"海尔伯格爵士手下的神秘炼金术士尼莱扎所著，自传三部曲之一。极为稀有的手稿，从未出版。",en:"One of three volumes covering the autobiography of Nileza, a mysterious alchemist in the service of Count Harebourg. This extremely rare manuscript has yet to be published."};
descriptions["16490"]={cn:"这堆文件是塞拉写的。里面夹着一封书信，笔迹华丽。看上去十分古老。",en:"It\'s very popular among the Hunters of Frigost Island, as they like to keep their things nice and warm! It all seems extremely old."};
descriptions["16491"]={cn:"当心手被冻僵！",en:"Get your nose stuck in a book and your tongue stuck on a shelf with this luxurious frozen bookcase."};
descriptions["16497"]={cn:"那萨满又赖账跑了，不用猜一定又躲在他家床底下呢。\n- 阿尔伯特",en:"The first place to look for a Masqueraider who\'s run off without paying his bill is under his bed.\n- Alibert -"};
descriptions["16498"]={cn:"那天，我早上醒来发现这个吉祥物就站在我边上发了狂地大叫着，太可怕了！",en:"This one time, I woke up and this charm was standing over me, snarling with rage, and it was sooo scary!"};
descriptions["16499"]={cn:"哦哦哦，好漂亮的柜子！我们来看看里面都放了些什么？我了个...抽屉钉死了！这人有病啊！",en:"Ohohoho, a beautiful dresser! What could be in here? *clunk* The drawers are nailed shut! What kind of lunatic would do something like that?"};
descriptions["16500"]={cn:"我的屏风屏了你的风。",en:"I screen, you screen, they all screen for my screen. \nGo and have a look. You first; I insist."};
descriptions["16501"]={cn:"这个东西...真糟糕...",en:"This one definitely leads to Bizarnia! *bump*\nAwww..."};
descriptions["16502"]={cn:"很有型，有型的意思就是...会亮。",en:"This lamp is super stylish, if by stylish you mean \'it emits light.\'"};
descriptions["16503"]={cn:"萨满梳妆只要一秒钟，换个面具就得了！",en:"The best thing about being a Masqueraider is that you can just pull on another face when you\'re feeling down in the mouth!"};
descriptions["16504"]={cn:"看清楚了，这桌子是圆的而不是方的，为了防撞，萨满实在是太小心谨慎了。",en:"Cowardly Masqueraiders hate bashing into things and hurting themselves during speed training, which is probably why this table is round rather than square."};
descriptions["16505"]={cn:"游戏的目标通过询问对手面具的各种特征来猜出对手到底戴了哪一种面具。",en:"The goal of the game is to spot your opponent\'s masked character out of a bunch of Masqueraiders by asking questions about their physical appearance. Hmmm..."};
descriptions["16506"]={cn:"如果，每个人，每一天都为街坊种上一盆花，那么十二世界将会变成美好的人间。",en:"If, every day, every citizen of the World of Twelve placed a flower somewhere his neighbor would find it, the World would be a much nicer place. Sadida proverb"};
descriptions["16507"]={cn:"穿上这套衣服你就厉害啦？并不。",en:"This costume won\'t make you a prodigy!"};
descriptions["16508"]={cn:"总是留下一条可疑的痕迹！",en:"It will leave a suspicious trail!"};
