descriptions["16757"]={cn:"可爱的小公仔，使你的小床每天都吱吱作响。",en:"A squeeze-and-sniff buddy who\'ll take the blame for your bed being squelchy every morning!"};
descriptions["16758"]={cn:"把戒指戴上，这样你就有借口整天吮手指了。",en:"Jam this on your thumb. At least then you\'ll have an excuse for sucking it all the time."};
descriptions["16759"]={cn:"好像一只碗扣在了头上。",en:"You feel like a little goldfish in a bowl with no water."};
descriptions["16760"]={cn:"这双靴子在经过的地方流下彩色的泡泡，同时吱吱作响。不过挺舒服的。",en:"These boots bubble and squeak all over the place. It\'s surprisingly comforting!"};
descriptions["16761"]={cn:"薄荷味的，你的胸一定很凉爽。",en:"With minty freshness like this on it all day, your torso will be a better kisser than you!"};
descriptions["16762"]={cn:"柠檬味，嘎嘣脆！",en:"When life gives you Lemon Jellies, make a Lemon Jelly Amulet!"};
descriptions["16763"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["16764"]={cn:"这是唯一能让你把者喱从牙缝里挑出来的东西。",en:"There\'s no better way to get a Jelly out of your grill."};
descriptions["16765"]={cn:"麦秆上还沾着几滴陈年鸡尾酒。敌人即便不被击中也会变得醉醺醺的。",en:"This oversized straw still contains drops of week-old cocktail, meaning it splatters your enemies with sticky unpleasantness as well as doing them physical harm."};
descriptions["16767"]={cn:"给敌人留下满嘴苦涩。",en:"To leave enemies with a sour taste in their mouth."};
descriptions["16768"]={cn:"难道你真的以为这条项链会让鼻子变长？少喝点！",en:"Did you really believe this amulet would make your nose grow? You should stop drinking so much."};
descriptions["16769"]={cn:"小姐你好蓝啊！",en:"Blue is totally your color!"};
descriptions["16770"]={cn:"人人都爱！",en:"Everyone\'s favorite!"};
descriptions["16771"]={cn:"一不小心就会从指上滑落，不过你应该庆幸能够拥有它。",en:"Sure, it\'ll slip through your fingers in no time, but you should be honored that you\'re even allowed to hold it!"};
descriptions["16772"]={cn:"这条腰带立志模仿者环王。现在你可以把者环王带在腰上了！",en:"This social outcast of a belt decided to try to become cool by imitating the Gelano. Now, you too can try to be cool by pretending your Gelano fits around your waist."};
descriptions["16773"]={cn:"鸡尾酒要摇匀，而不是搅拌。你又不是调酒师，管那么多干嘛？",en:"Cocktails are better shaken, not stirred, but since when did you know anything about good taste?"};
descriptions["16774"]={cn:"柔软有弹性，皇家者喱肩甲是生活的理想伴侣。",en:"Soft, squelchy, and full of fun, Smoothettes are the best way to put a little bounce back in your life!"};
descriptions["16775"]={cn:"本来这是双长筒靴，前主人十分热爱甜食，所以...",en:"These boots used to be thigh-high, but the previous owner got the munchies..."};
descriptions["16776"]={cn:"品质出众！不许吃！",en:"As noble as they come!"};
descriptions["16777"]={cn:"不许笑...",en:"This crown makes your brain look funny..."};
descriptions["16778"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["16779"]={cn:"专为舞王准备！特别是者喱吃多了的舞王！",en:"A professional dancer toiled tirelessly to collect this extract from somewhere close to a Jelly\'s heart! A few drops should suffice."};
descriptions["16781"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sandy substance contained in this flask! A few grains should suffice."};
descriptions["16782"]={cn:"必须经过加工才能使用。",en:"This skin needs to be refined into leather before you can use it to create equipment."};
descriptions["16783"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["16784"]={cn:"柔软的沙子，散发着金子般的耀眼光芒。",en:"Sand so fine and bright that it looks like tiny particles of gold."};
descriptions["16785"]={cn:"这块鱼鳞受到沙子的严重侵蚀，表面上还残留着不少沙粒。",en:"This scale has been quite damaged by the sand. There are even a few grains of it stuck on its surface."};
descriptions["16786"]={cn:"面对沙滩，然后扑倒：这是炫耀披风的一种方式。",en:"Lie on your front on the beach: it\'s an adventurer sand-wich!"};
descriptions["16787"]={cn:"这就是你的胸甲了...别以为没人看到你在胸前放了两个沙袋！",en:"This is the one for you... Don\'t think we haven\'t seen you making six-packs and womanly curves out of sand on the beach!"};
descriptions["16788"]={cn:"能让你在海滩上像个者喱一样跳来跳去！",en:"These boots will have you hopping along the beach like a Jelly!"};
descriptions["16789"]={cn:"由流沙制成。现在你可以不用洗手了。",en:"This ring is made of sand. A great reason to stop washing your hands."};
descriptions["16790"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["16791"]={cn:"再深的水现在你也能游上岸了！当然前提是你离岸很近。",en:"Now you can swim safely in even the deepest waters (as long as you stay near the top)."};
descriptions["16792"]={cn:"好酷的船长铁钩！",en:"Is that a captain\'s hook? Good form!"};
descriptions["16793"]={cn:"这样一来你可以轻松获得玩沙大赛！",en:"You could win the sandcastle competition in this any day!"};
descriptions["16794"]={cn:"拿来在海滩边玩切西瓜游戏，不是切人游戏！",en:"For playing \"who can spear the ball first\" by the water\'s edge."};
descriptions["16795"]={cn:"曾经是米奇·软泡的收藏品。由松软的泡泡制成，只能抵挡沙尘...",en:"Despite being a favorite with Mitch Loosecannon, this board is made of foam and won\'t protect you from anything more than blowing sand."};
descriptions["16796"]={cn:"里面的确藏了一朵玫瑰。只是不知道为什么，项链散发出沙子和小便的气味...一定很适合你。",en:"This delicate rose is made of a subtle blend of sand and urine. Suits you."};
descriptions["16797"]={cn:"这颗珍珠在怪物的嘴里呆了很久，染上了怪异的颜色。",en:"This pearl has spent such a long time in the monster\'s mouth that it\'s absorbed some of the color."};
descriptions["16798"]={cn:"原来你在海滩边上买的高价货也不都是假的！",en:"For once, the overpriced tat you bought on holiday isn\'t half bad!"};
descriptions["16799"]={cn:"今晚，尽情跳舞！",en:"Tonight we\'re gonna party like it\'s 599!"};
descriptions["16800"]={cn:"没有人见过颜色如此多彩的盾...",en:"This shield would have made a great palette for budding painters - if only it didn\'t let in so much water."};
descriptions["16801"]={cn:"用来勾引敌人，就算不起作用你也觉得很好玩！",en:"You love teasing your enemies with this thing, and you don\'t care if they don\'t find it funny!"};
descriptions["16802"]={cn:"现在你有地方存放重要文件了。只是文件会变得湿漉漉的。",en:"This belt has room for you to store your important documents, as long as you don\'t mind them getting all salty and wet."};
descriptions["16803"]={cn:"有这样的指环，全世界都变得真棒。",en:"With a ring like this, the world is your oyster!"};
descriptions["16804"]={cn:"有人在你背上吐了？真的有人在你背上吐了？",en:"Did someone throw up on your back? It looks like someone threw up on your back."};
descriptions["16805"]={cn:"你的妆掉了...都掉到肩甲上了！",en:"Your make-up is running... really badly... all the way to your shoulders."};
descriptions["16806"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["16808"]={cn:"一位勇敢的牧民收集了这种派对残渣！只要几滴就能起效。",en:"A fearless trapper mineswept tirelessly to collect the party leftovers contained in this flask! A few drops should suffice."};
descriptions["16809"]={cn:"这种粘液出产于某些你想不到的地方。别瞎猜了...",en:"This slobber has been scraped out of a place you\'re lucky you\'ve never seen. It\'s no use guessing... The truth is more horrible than you could ever imagine!"};
descriptions["16810"]={cn:"由于不受沙子和海水的侵蚀，这种布被频繁用作船上的帆布。用坏后还可以拿来当伞！",en:"Resistant to sand and sea water, this fabric is often used in the manufacture of sails. When it gets too ripped and worn, you can always use it to make an umbrella for someone you hate."};
descriptions["16811"]={cn:"者喱男孩喝下太多海水，满嘴口臭。",en:"The Bilbiboyz swallow so much water while they\'re rehearsing that they tend to have smelly, salty breath."};
descriptions["16812"]={cn:"即便你在海面上睡着了，也不会沉下去。去试试看！",en:"Even if you\'re in a trance, you won\'t go under! Practical, aren\'t they? Practical, no?"};
descriptions["16813"]={cn:"脚趾放松，全身放松。",en:"You know that summer\'s finally here when you feel the sand between your toes."};
descriptions["16814"]={cn:"再也不用担心被突然丢到海滩上了！",en:"With this towel on, there\'s no need to fear getting thrown on your back on the hot sand."};
descriptions["16815"]={cn:"日夜保护您。",en:"Protects from Yoovie rays and boogie nights."};
descriptions["16816"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["16817"]={cn:"大家都穿着这样的底裤上街...我是认真的！",en:"All the cool kids are wearing them... Honest!"};
descriptions["16818"]={cn:"人们都穿着泳衣上街...我说真的！",en:"All the cool kids are wearing them... Honest!"};
descriptions["16819"]={cn:"用者喱泡沫制成，极易浮于水面之上。",en:"This tube of gelatinous foam is very useful for learning to swim."};
descriptions["16820"]={cn:"老天爷...你做了些什么？！我早说过只在紧急的时候才能使用！",en:"Oh buoy... What did I tell you? Only pull the cord in an emergency... or a particularly sticky encounter!"};
descriptions["16821"]={cn:"你的朋友们一定会全都盯着卡牌上的漂亮花纹的，他们甚至不会注意到你偷吃了薯片。",en:"Your buddies will be so impressed by the beautiful design on these cards that they won\'t even notice you swiping their chips."};
descriptions["16822"]={cn:"夏天里穿短背心以展示肌肉，猛男的绝佳伙伴。",en:"This cool summer tank top will allow you to show off your biceps while beating on people who make inappropriate jokes. Party on, dudes!"};
descriptions["16823"]={cn:"有人已经咬掉了一块！素质真差...",en:"Somebody already took a chomp of this Jelly! Such bad taste..."};
descriptions["16824"]={cn:"释放你内心的者喱！",en:"Free your inner Jelly!"};
descriptions["16825"]={cn:"虽然由甜品制作而成，但并不代表这柄剑没有杀伤力。",en:"This thing can\'t be dangerous, can it? It\'s used for serving up snacks... Make sure you\'re not the next one!"};
descriptions["16826"]={cn:"可伸缩，随时可以放进口袋里。缺点是想用的时候至少需要1分钟才能变成原来大小...",en:"The great thing about this sword is that it\'ll fit in your pocket to be whipped out at the first sign of danger. Too bad it takes at least a minute to inflate..."};
descriptions["16827"]={cn:"这是你们要的新装备...",en:"Awww... You asked for a giraffe!"};
descriptions["16828"]={cn:"戴上护符，你感觉头变得和喱维萨女王一样大。她可不会原谅你！",en:"Your head has swollen up pretty bad ever since you started wearing the same amulet as the Bilby Queen. Will she ever forgive you for biting her style?"};
descriptions["16829"]={cn:"副作用是会让你耳聋。反正开派对，随便了。",en:"One of this helmet\'s side effects is that it leaves you stone deaf. Not necessarily a bad thing on a party island!"};
descriptions["16830"]={cn:"塔吉贝穿过...",en:"Like water off a duck\'s... shoulders."};
descriptions["16831"]={cn:"在你和舞伴之间保持安全距离。",en:"These shorts will keep a respectable distance between you and your partner on the dancefloor."};
descriptions["16832"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["16833"]={cn:"先告诉老妈你在复习功课，然后溜出去参加舞会！",en:"Tell your parents you\'re studying, then go dance the night away like the crazy jelly you are!"};
descriptions["16834"]={cn:"直接到达者喱皇帝统治下的者喱维度。",en:"Direct access to the dimension governed by Emperor Jellix."};
descriptions["16835"]={cn:"在者喱的尖叫声中，蜜胶树重新焕发了活力。",en:"This gummy lump moves and sways in time with the Jellies\' cries."};
descriptions["16837"]={cn:"需用数吨糖水浇灌。",en:"A sweet little plant that needs tons of attention and sugared water."};
descriptions["16839"]={cn:"纪念你曾经让珍蚌珠找不着珍珠。",en:"A battle trophy to remind you of your victory in the dungeon."};
descriptions["16841"]={cn:"纪念你曾经让者喱皇帝成功瘦身。",en:"A battle trophy to remind you of your victory in the dungeon."};
descriptions["16842"]={cn:"前往者喱派对！\n打开地图，找到小船！",en:"Head for the Full Jellix Party!\nCheck your map to find the boat!"};
descriptions["16843"]={cn:"很明显是某棵小树上的碎片。",en:"This appears to be a piece from a sweet, gummy little tree."};
descriptions["16845"]={cn:"仍然可以嚼两下，完全停不下来！",en:"This leftover gum can still be eaten by those who throw caution to the wind. Five hour rule!"};
descriptions["16849"]={cn:"能令一棵特殊的树木起死回生。",en:"This extract should bring a very special tree back to life."};
descriptions["16850"]={cn:"个头很小，但重达一吨，所以与一吨黄金等价！",en:"Even though it might be small, this Krakotte weighs a ton and is worth its weight in gold!"};
descriptions["16851"]={cn:"宠物染料可以于宠物设定介面中更改。此物品已无用处，可以将其分解掉。",en:"Pet colorings can be changed in the pet settings interface. This item is obsolete; you can recycle it."};
descriptions["16852"]={cn:"看到黄金独角小仙意味着好运。你踩到狗屎运了，老兄！",en:"It\'s pretty rare to see a Golden Scarafly around these parts! You lucky devil, you!"};
descriptions["16853"]={cn:"宠物染料可以于宠物设定介面中更改。此物品已无用处，可以将其分解掉。",en:"Pet colorings can be changed in the pet settings interface. This item is obsolete; you can recycle it."};
descriptions["16854"]={cn:"一只移动储蓄罐，存钱容易取钱难...",en:"A walking piggy bank! Putting money in\'s easier than getting it back out..."};
descriptions["16855"]={cn:"晶亮又新鲜，分量刚好一顿饭！",en:"It\'s nice, it\'s fresh, and it\'s almost enough for a snack!"};
