descriptions["16877"]={cn:"石头一样沉重！",en:"Aside from their unquestionable utility as boots, they can also be used in a pinch as a bludgeon."};
descriptions["16878"]={cn:"没有老母护肩那么珍贵，但也不失为一件好装备。",en:"While less flamboyant than Mamagmulettes, the Stalagettes are a must for rock n\' roll parties."};
descriptions["16879"]={cn:"这到底是石笋老母的哪个部位，科学界一直没有定论。人们猜测这是她的...指甲！",en:"Many a scientist has asked themselves what part of the Mamagmote this is - the answer is simple: it\'s a nail!"};
descriptions["16880"]={cn:"因为石笋老母而膨胀起来的石笋。",en:"A good beating stick made out of a Mamagmote pumped with hormones."};
descriptions["16881"]={cn:"像有魔力一般地配合着你的腰。",en:"This Mamagmote cerebral column, encrusted with magnetic stones, is perfectly suited to the size of your tiny waist."};
descriptions["16882"]={cn:"原本脆弱的笋变得像石头一样坚硬，从里到外的坚硬。",en:"Even the Mamagmote\'s internal organs are protected by a rocky exoskeleton, like this heart valve."};
descriptions["16883"]={cn:"为什么石笋领主和石笋老母之间不能有爱的抱抱？",en:"The Stalagmonarch\'s Spike that the Mamagmote kept with love..."};
descriptions["16884"]={cn:"这么逼真，你不禁怀疑这是用什么材质做的。",en:"The texture of this miniature is so realistic that you\'d prefer not to know what it\'s made out of."};
descriptions["16885"]={cn:"当年人们流行拥有宽厚的肩膀，那时这种护肩非常畅销，以至于差点导致石笋灭绝。",en:"These large epaulettes were quite popular in the 970s, and almost caused the disappearance of the Mamagmotes for good."};
descriptions["16886"]={cn:"石笋老母的那一层岩浆让你的脚永远保持温暖，即便在大热天！",en:"Carved directly out of the Mamagmote\'s magmatic breastplate, these Mamagboots will keep you warm all winter! And all summer too!"};
descriptions["16887"]={cn:"跟我们不同，石笋并没有大脑，而是由大量的中枢神经负责思考。后来就被工匠做成了护符，据说戴上有神奇的疗效。",en:"The Mamagmote doesn\'t have a brain as such, but rather multiple major nerve clusters. Artisans don\'t care which nerves they use to craft. So your Mamagmulette could as easily be responsible for the Mamagmote\'s asymmetric vision as for the control of its sphincters..."};
descriptions["16888"]={cn:"虽然说是老母头盔，实际上是石笋宝宝出生的时候那些顶破的蛋壳做的。那么蛋是从哪里来的呢？",en:"Although its name may lead you to believe it\'s a helmet, it\'s actually the skull of a stalagmote fetus from an egg ripped from the Mamagmote\'s abdomen."};
descriptions["16889"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["16890"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["16891"]={cn:"有巨魔的大腿那么重，举起来就要耗尽你的所有力气。",en:"As heavy as an adult Trool\'s leg, this mace should get you sweating if nothing else."};
descriptions["16892"]={cn:"巨魔穿起来显得高大威猛，你穿起来却猥琐得像绿皮。",en:"This cloak looked elegant on the Trool it came from, but it just makes you look like a deformed Bwork."};
descriptions["16893"]={cn:"用于储藏食物，以备不时之需。",en:"This belt used to be used to store snacks for those anxious moments."};
descriptions["16894"]={cn:"不错的战斗时装。但是没必要天天穿，除非你每天都在战斗。",en:"Troolish Shoulderguards are designed for use in battles of attrition. There\'s no need to wear them all day, every day, unless you see life as a constant battle."};
descriptions["16895"]={cn:"授予巨魔学院的最终赢家。",en:"This mask is awarded to the winner of Trool Academy."};
descriptions["16896"]={cn:"授予巨魔学院的最终赢家。",en:"This ring is awarded to the winner of Trool Academy."};
descriptions["16897"]={cn:"授予巨魔学院的最终赢家。",en:"This cloak is awarded to the winner of Trool Academy."};
descriptions["16898"]={cn:"授予巨魔学院的最终赢家。",en:"These boots are awarded to the winner of Trool Academy."};
descriptions["16899"]={cn:"坚实的防护源于超高的质量。这面盾足有半个巨魔的分量。只有力量够强的冒险者才举得起来。",en:"With great resistance comes great density. This shield weighs half a Trool, so it\'ll only protect you if you\'re really strong already."};
descriptions["16900"]={cn:"授予巨魔学院的赢家。然而，市场上马上就会出现无数的仿冒品。",en:"This weapon was the Trool Academy champion\'s lucky charm. When he became popular, the market was suddenly flooded with cheap rip-offs."};
descriptions["16901"]={cn:"哞哞腰带？不，只是巨魔的内裤。穿上试试！",en:"A Moogrr leash? Nope, a Trool\'s underpants. Try them on!"};
descriptions["16902"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["16903"]={cn:"死亡不是结束，而是另一段旅程的开始。",en:"Death is just the beginning of the end."};
descriptions["16904"]={cn:"好巨魔离不开好腰带。",en:"A good workman never blames his Trools."};
descriptions["16905"]={cn:"胜利源自努力。",en:"Victory is born of effort."};
descriptions["16906"]={cn:"努力源于思想的一瞬之间。",en:"Effort is no more than a state of mind."};
descriptions["16908"]={cn:"柔韧的泡泡，保护你的胸口不受伤害。",en:"This bubble of Jelly will protect your body from nasty outside threats."};
descriptions["16909"]={cn:"柔韧的泡泡，保护你的胸口不受伤害。",en:"This bubble of Jelly will protect your body from nasty outside threats."};
descriptions["16912"]={cn:"泡泡...泡泡...砰！",en:"Bobbing along... Bobbing along... POP!"};
descriptions["16913"]={cn:"泡泡...泡泡...砰！",en:"Bobbing along... Bobbing along... POP!"};
descriptions["16918"]={cn:"只要一出门，脚趾上就会粘上黄沙，但是发出的吱吱声却很悦耳！",en:"These open-toed boots will get sand all over them as soon as you step outside, but you love the squelching sound they make."};
descriptions["16919"]={cn:"只要一出门，脚趾上就会粘上黄沙，但是发出的吱吱声却很悦耳！",en:"These open-toed boots will get sand all over them as soon as you step outside, but you love the squelching sound they make."};
descriptions["16929"]={cn:"智商低到永远追随你每一次九死一生的冒险，正像你的骑士伙伴。",en:"This adorable pet will be loyal even in your craziest adventures!"};
