descriptions["16942"]={cn:"可以创建公会。快去各城市的公会大厅一探究竟吧。",en:"The Guildalogem allows you to create a guild for free. To do so, head to the Guild-o-Mats located in cities."};
descriptions["16945"]={cn:"白衣胜雪，一尘不染！",en:"A Piwi that\'s whiter than white - you won\'t get any dirt on this one!"};
descriptions["16948"]={cn:"你将恶棍统统砍成肉片，串成香肠在家门口叫卖！",en:"You make mincemeat of Villains! And then, just to make sure they don\'t come back to bother you, you pack the meat into sausage casing and eat them raw!"};
descriptions["16950"]={cn:"你也可以开着这辆火车去扫平世上的邪恶。",en:"Tear along the train tracks just like you tear up the World\'s bad guys!"};
descriptions["16951"]={cn:"这么昂贵的床一般只能在有钱商人的庇护领地中才能看到，跟你那间茅屋可不配。",en:"Beds like these are usually seen in expensive manors belonging to rich businessmen. What\'s it doing in your little hovel?"};
descriptions["16952"]={cn:"那天，整个萨弗基亚都在讨论海滩上搁浅的鲸鱼，到头来只不过是个机器玩意儿，太令人失望了！",en:"This one time, the whole of Sufokia was alive with talk of a beached whale that had arrived at the harbor. In the end, it was actually a mechanical creature, and we were sooo disappointed!"};
descriptions["16953"]={cn:"睡觉时要把七零八落的金属零件放床头。",en:"Nuts and bolts, amps and volts, that\'s what makes the World go round!"};
descriptions["16954"]={cn:"其实蒸汽行者没什么好掩藏的，不过嘛...有用白不用。",en:"Foggernauts don\'t appear to have much to hide, but they\'re all as modest as can be. but they\'re all as modest as can be. Curiouser and curiouser."};
descriptions["16955"]={cn:"金属制品放在里面可以一直保持鲜亮如新，好东西！",en:"A wardrobe with a built-in polishing machine to keep your metal accessories bright and shiny - insta-glint!"};
descriptions["16956"]={cn:"毁灭晶体可能是世界上最不稳定的物质了，因此请勿使这盏灯靠近汽油...干草...和水...还有空气...",en:"Stasis is probably the most unstable substance in existence. Don\'t hold this lamp anywhere near petrol... or hay... or water... or air..."};
descriptions["16957"]={cn:"你觉得蒸汽行者不用梳妆吗？天真！",en:"You think Foggernauts don\'t spend time getting ready? Oh, if only you knew..."};
descriptions["16958"]={cn:"蒸汽行者的家具都有一股特别的气味，混合着灌木和海鲜的味道，怎么回事呢？",en:"All Foggernaut furniture has a peculiar odor; a delicate blend of spindrift and crustaceans. Oh wait... the bottom of the table is covered in barnacles. That would explain it."};
descriptions["16959"]={cn:"玩法是想办法弄沉对手的船，这种玩法最近很受欢迎。",en:"The idea is to try to sink your opponent\'s ships by finding them on a grid. Psh... Like that concept is ever gonna get popular!"};
descriptions["16960"]={cn:"这里的植物很奇怪啊。如果有蒸汽飘过，它就会咔嚓咔嚓的扭动起来。",en:"This plant is the playful sort: it reacts comically to all sorts of external steam-uli. Cap\'n Chafer told me that one... KLAK KLAK KLAK!"};
descriptions["16961"]={cn:"纪念你曾经将喀努斯一顿海扁。",en:"A battle trophy to remind you of that one time when you banished Excarnus to Excarnam."};
descriptions["16962"]={cn:"纪念你曾经让米尔卡吼叫着找妈。",en:"A battle trophy to remind you of that one time when you made Milkar howl for his mommy."};
descriptions["16963"]={cn:"纪念你击落黑鸦骑士的英勇事迹。",en:"A battle trophy to remind you of that one time when you made the Black Crow into an eiderdown."};
descriptions["16964"]={cn:"纪念你曾经成功踢馆，弹龙猪的尾巴弹到死。",en:"At last! A battle trophy to remind you of that one time when you ground the Dragon Pig\'s bones to make your bread, and your pies, and your pasties... Lasted you six months, that carcass!"};
descriptions["16965"]={cn:"戴上这顶帽子，你会变成全城知名的肥猪！",en:"Wrap this rindy hat around your head and you\'ll be the BIG PIG around town!"};
descriptions["16966"]={cn:"可爱的靴子，将你的敌人料理成沙拉。",en:"Some lovely pork knuckles to serve up on a bed of salad."};
descriptions["16967"]={cn:"也许你太肥了，没法飞起来，不过穿在身上真好看！",en:"You\'re too porky to actually leave the ground, but they look good on you!"};
descriptions["16968"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["16969"]={cn:"猪头肉欧耶！",en:"Hamhead!"};
descriptions["16970"]={cn:"我正踏着猪肉行走...哇哦酷！",en:"I\'m walking on bacon... Woooaaah!"};
descriptions["16971"]={cn:"现在伟大的巨人就站在你的身旁，小不点。",en:"Now you have giants standing on your shoulders, dwarf."};
descriptions["16972"]={cn:"一件能够抵御任何扭曲的胸甲，同时它还具备特有的电台，只要你调频至\'N\'电台就可以每天都能听到有人在笑。",en:"Twist one of the wings on this thing and it\'ll tune you into Live \'n\' Lardy FM, the only radio station that will have you snorting with laughter all day long."};
descriptions["16973"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["16974"]={cn:"现在你可以在战斗中把双拳裹起来了！",en:"Now you can bandage up your fists for all those sweaty, porcine battles!"};
descriptions["16975"]={cn:"这条腰带并不能提供你20点行动力，但是还是很有用。",en:"Alas, it\'s no +20, but they say it\'s a relic handed down for generations, and that has to count for something."};
descriptions["16976"]={cn:"端庄得体，用于和大人物一起吃饭。",en:"Perfect when you\'re having someone dignified for dinner."};
descriptions["16977"]={cn:"猪也会念经！",en:"Letting you have this necklace kind of feels like casting pearls before swine."};
descriptions["16979"]={cn:"这张卷轴允许你转变为中立（不属于任何国家）。你可以选择维持中立，或前往阿斯图布的国家公告板选择新的国籍！",en:"Using this scroll will allow you to once more become Neutral (not affiliated with any Nation). You can then choose to remain Neutral, or to go to the Nation Board in Astrub to choose a new Nation!"};
