descriptions["17054"]={cn:"正义勇士，我是阿超！",en:"Show that you\'re an ULTRA JUSTICE FIGHTER!"};
descriptions["17055"]={cn:"正义勇士，我是阿宏！",en:"Show that you\'re a GIGA JUSTICE FIGHTER!"};
descriptions["17056"]={cn:"正义勇士，我是阿帅！",en:"Show that you\'re a SUPRA JUSTICE FIGHTER!"};
descriptions["17057"]={cn:"正义勇士，我是阿伟！",en:"Show that you\'re an ULTIMA JUSTICE FIGHTER!"};
descriptions["17058"]={cn:"正义勇士，我是阿酷！",en:"Show that you\'re a KROSMO JUSTICE FIGHTER!"};
descriptions["17059"]={cn:"别吃糖吃噎了，重复那个吃糖吃死的国王的悲剧！",en:"Don\'t choke on this candy. History\'s great, but there\'s no need to re-enact the Taking of the Pastille."};
descriptions["17060"]={cn:"让你的庇护袋里面看起来神圣一点，萨满必备。",en:"This sacred table will look great in your crib. Especially if you\'re a Masqueraider."};
descriptions["17061"]={cn:"这份文件授予你\"暗影看守\"称号。",en:"This document will enable you to prove your status as a Jailer of Shadows."};
descriptions["17069"]={cn:"小毛豆轻轻一抖，小屋的外形就被改变了。",en:"This Blueprint will enable you to change the appearance of your house in two shakes of a Rotcere\'s torso."};
descriptions["17070"]={cn:"小毛豆轻轻一抖，小屋的外形就被改变了。",en:"This Blueprint will enable you to change the appearance of your house in two shakes of a Rotcere\'s torso."};
descriptions["17071"]={cn:"小毛豆轻轻一抖，小屋的外形就被改变了。",en:"This Blueprint will enable you to change the appearance of your house in two shakes of a Rotcere\'s torso."};
descriptions["17072"]={cn:"小毛豆轻轻一抖，小屋的外形就被改变了。",en:"This Blueprint will enable you to change the appearance of your house in two shakes of a Rotcere\'s torso."};
descriptions["17073"]={cn:"我们都知道这个障碍的作用就是阻止人们破坏它另一边的事物。",en:"The barrier we all know and love for its ability to stop people breaking on through to the other side."};
descriptions["17074"]={cn:"左、左，右、右，转身，跳、跳、跳。",en:"Get ready to leap giddily through the fields in search of fresh Cawwots!"};
descriptions["17075"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few drops should suffice."};
descriptions["17076"]={cn:"必须经过加工才能使用。",en:"This radiant skin needs to be refined into leather before you can use it to create equipment."};
descriptions["17077"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["17078"]={cn:"必须经过加工才能使用。",en:"This pale skin needs to be refined into leather before you can use it to create equipment."};
descriptions["17079"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["17080"]={cn:"必须经过加工才能使用。",en:"This dark skin needs to be refined into leather before you can use it to create equipment."};
descriptions["17081"]={cn:"点击两下来把整组古代资源转换成新的资源。古代资源需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["17082"]={cn:"当心！如果一不小心溅在衣服上就永远洗不干净了！",en:"Careful: If you drop some on your clothes, you\'ll never get the stain out!"};
descriptions["17083"]={cn:"在日光下失去了原有的色彩。",en:"It must have lost its color in the daylight."};
descriptions["17084"]={cn:"时不时释放出些许毒气。",en:"This miniature releases little puffs of noxious gas to remind you of your adventures."};
descriptions["17085"]={cn:"神赐予的礼物，用于隐藏你的私密日记。",en:"This hollow miniature is a godsend for hiding your diary in."};
descriptions["17086"]={cn:"一尊神圣雕像。",en:"A hollow miniature."};
descriptions["17087"]={cn:"吓人咧。",en:"A hollow miniature."};
descriptions["17088"]={cn:"吓人咧。",en:"A hollow miniature."};
descriptions["17089"]={cn:"一尊神圣的雕像。",en:"A hollow miniature."};
descriptions["17090"]={cn:"即便是一尊雕像，莱拉公主也在鄙视着你。",en:"Even in miniature version, she still manages to look down on you."};
descriptions["17091"]={cn:"记得千万不要让你的狼朋友们看到这个雕像。",en:"Keep this miniature out of sight of your Boowolf friends."};
descriptions["17092"]={cn:"总觉得好像复活了...",en:"It almost looks as though it might come to life..."};
descriptions["17093"]={cn:"尖刺看上去栩栩如生。",en:"The stinger on this thing looks almost as lethal as the real one."};
descriptions["17094"]={cn:"被格斗爱好者广泛使用。",en:"This iron helmet is frequently worn by close-combat fighters."};
descriptions["17095"]={cn:"保护你的颈部不受攻击。",en:"This helmet covers your throat to protect it from your opponent\'s blows."};
descriptions["17096"]={cn:"在战斗中好好表现，它会让你心想事成。",en:"Rent out your services during battles, and this helmet will get even."};
descriptions["17097"]={cn:"不会叫的鸡才会下蛋。",en:"The wise don\'t think aloud. Seriously. Stop it."};
descriptions["17098"]={cn:"给你家一般舒适的感觉。",en:"You\'ll feel right at home wearing this helmet."};
descriptions["17099"]={cn:"戴着那么耀眼的头盔，就必须带头冲锋陷阵。",en:"Take charge and lead your allies into battle. They\'ll definitely see you in this helmet."};
descriptions["17100"]={cn:"为了方便呼吸，头盔上特意开了口，不过要当心，千万别让敌人攻击这个开口...",en:"This helmet is open in places to let your head breathe. Be careful not to receive any blows through the openings though..."};
descriptions["17101"]={cn:"错误的认知往往比无知更可怕。",en:"Beware of false knowledge; it is more dangerous than ignorance."};
descriptions["17102"]={cn:"对敌人的残忍就是对自己的仁慈。",en:"Try to put an end to hostilities... by any means necessary."};
descriptions["17103"]={cn:"不但轻便，而且实用，能帮你抵御各种伤害。",en:"This lightly-vaulted helmet will resist all projectiles that come your way."};
descriptions["17104"]={cn:"脱下头盔，洗洗睡吧。",en:"When you take this helmet off, it\'s extinction time."};
descriptions["17105"]={cn:"智慧可不仅仅是书本里的知识。",en:"\"Wisdom is not wisdom when it is derived from books alone.\""};
descriptions["17106"]={cn:"只要你不参加战斗，这件胸甲就能保你毫发无损。",en:"This breastplate offers great protection, so long as you stay away from the battle."};
descriptions["17107"]={cn:"非常漂亮的护胸，尤其适合持久战。",en:"A very nice breastplate to wear, especially when the battle drags on."};
descriptions["17108"]={cn:"由精铜打造，适用于任何危险场合。",en:"Made of articulated copper blades, this armor adapts to any dangerous situation."};
descriptions["17109"]={cn:"安心，一切都好。即使不好，也没什么。",en:"It is wisest to keep one\'s organs within oneself."};
descriptions["17110"]={cn:"正面被加固，能弹开敌人的攻击...但愿吧...",en:"This breastplate is padded in the front, which will make projectiles bounce off... you hope."};
descriptions["17111"]={cn:"超合金强化，几乎无法刺穿。",en:"This breastplate is completely reinforced. It would be very difficult to get through it."};
descriptions["17112"]={cn:"精铁打造的护甲，为保护主人而承受的累累伤痕清晰可见。",en:"This breastplate made entirely of iron protects its wearer, but it keeps all the dings from each hit."};
descriptions["17113"]={cn:"爱情和理智不可兼得。",en:"It is impossible to love and to be wise."};
descriptions["17114"]={cn:"选材实惠，制作简单，穿戴方便。",en:"This armor is made of wooden planks and leather, providing simple-to-use and easy-to-make protection."};
descriptions["17115"]={cn:"没有男式和女式之分，穿戴者的身体需自行适应这件胸甲。",en:"Whether it\'s a man or a woman wearing it, this breastplate doesn\'t change shape: It\'s the wearer\'s body that adapts to fit."};
descriptions["17116"]={cn:"给予你无语伦比的力量，令敌人恐惧不已。",en:"This armor is dreaded by your enemies, because it gives unequaled strength to its wielder."};
descriptions["17117"]={cn:"仁者无敌。",en:"A loving heart is the truest wisdom."};
descriptions["17118"]={cn:"让你的敌人痛苦不堪，对你敬而远之。",en:"This cape will give your enemies a hard time. They\'d best keep their distance."};
descriptions["17119"]={cn:"保护你的颈部和肩部。",en:"This cape will protect your neck and shoulders from attacks."};
descriptions["17120"]={cn:"它会陪伴你直至旅程的终点。",en:"This cape will serve your needs until the end of your adventure."};
descriptions["17121"]={cn:"聪明的人善于问正确的问题。比如，这件披风是正宗的吗？",en:"A prudent question is one half of wisdom. For example, is this cape genuine?"};
descriptions["17122"]={cn:"身轻如燕，如鱼得水。",en:"This cape\'s weight, or lack thereof, will help you in battle. Your movements will be that much more fluid."};
descriptions["17123"]={cn:"这件披风非常喜欢战斗的快感。",en:"This cape finds pleasure in the middle of the battlefield."};
descriptions["17124"]={cn:"这件披风是由一种轻羊毛制成的，穿上它简直帅呆了。",en:"This cape is made from a very light veil of wool. It\'ll give you a certain style."};
descriptions["17125"]={cn:"真相偏爱热爱冒险的人。",en:"The truth is not for all men, but only for those who seek it."};
descriptions["17126"]={cn:"穿上披风，保护你的背后不受敌人攻击。",en:"Keep a layer of protection between your back and your enemies\' attacks with this cape."};
descriptions["17127"]={cn:"让你的气场变得强大，但是穿戴起来不太方便。",en:"This cape gives you an authoritarian look, but the cut isn\'t very accommodating."};
descriptions["17128"]={cn:"一声怒吼，恫退敌人。",en:"Wait until your enemy is in range before you cry wolf."};
descriptions["17129"]={cn:"耐心是智慧之友。",en:"Patience is the companion of wisdom."};
descriptions["17130"]={cn:"记载了你冒险之路上的点点滴滴。",en:"This fabric amulet displays several decorations you got during your numerous adventures."};
descriptions["17131"]={cn:"戴上它，你连衣服都不用穿。",en:"This amulet aspires to be the one and only thing you wear."};
descriptions["17132"]={cn:"佩戴守望护符是一种至高无上的荣耀。",en:"It\'s an honor just to wear this amulet!"};
descriptions["17133"]={cn:"聪明人都会保持颈部温暖。",en:"It is wise to keep your neck warm."};
descriptions["17134"]={cn:"谨以此护符表彰你的功勋。",en:"This amulet may become very dear to you."};
descriptions["17135"]={cn:"这个坠饰对你来说举足轻重。",en:"This amulet may come to have a very important spot among your equipment."};
descriptions["17136"]={cn:"勇气的象征，你当之无愧。",en:"This amulet serves as a well-deserved medal."};
descriptions["17137"]={cn:"进步是从了解自己有多无知开始的。",en:"The only true wisdom is in knowing you know nothing."};
descriptions["17138"]={cn:"这个护符能制造创生力脉冲，你可以利用它发射信号。",en:"This amulet generates a little pulse of Wakfu, allowing you to send out a signal."};
descriptions["17139"]={cn:"随便拿，随便用。",en:"This amulet is there for whoever wants to grab it."};
descriptions["17140"]={cn:"它喜欢藏在衣服右边的口袋里。",en:"This metallic amulet is frequently hidden in the right-hand pocket of a jacket."};
descriptions["17141"]={cn:"显然，你需要更多悟性。",en:"Wisdom comes with experience, which you still lack."};
descriptions["17142"]={cn:"裹得严严实实才能上战场。",en:"Nothing better for keeping covered during the battle."};
descriptions["17143"]={cn:"都给我停下！",en:"These epaulettes are said to stop anything."};
descriptions["17144"]={cn:"穿上它，用肩膀顶几下敌人，他就无力反击你了。",en:"A few hits with your shoulder will be enough to flatten your enemy."};
descriptions["17145"]={cn:"永远保持清醒，无论是真的还是装的。",en:"It is not wise to lose your head, either figuratively or literally."};
descriptions["17146"]={cn:"能免疫任何攻击...？",en:"These epaulettes offer all-purpose immunity."};
descriptions["17147"]={cn:"不惜任何代价保护主人！",en:"To defend their wearer, these epaulettes will jump right into the fray!"};
descriptions["17148"]={cn:"虽然穿着不便，但能为你提供强有力的保护。",en:"These epaulettes are difficult to wear, but provide unparalleled protection."};
descriptions["17149"]={cn:"智慧是你知道接下来做什么；而坚持做下去才是真品质。",en:"Wisdom is knowing what to do next; virtue is doing it."};
descriptions["17150"]={cn:"能分摊你身体的重量，以减轻背部劳损。",en:"These epaulettes take your back problems into consideration and redistribute your weight."};
descriptions["17151"]={cn:"这个肩甲让接近你的人化成灰。",en:"These epaulettes will turn anyone who comes close into powder."};
descriptions["17152"]={cn:"动脑子的要比动手的更长命。",en:"Wisdom is always an overmatch for strength."};
descriptions["17153"]={cn:"穿上这件肩甲就等于全副武装了。",en:"Once these epaulettes are equipped, you\'ll be heavily armed."};
descriptions["17154"]={cn:"它愿为你付出一切。",en:"This belt will give its all to help your cause."};
descriptions["17155"]={cn:"这根腰带会为你带来忠实的拥护者。",en:"This belt has sworn unflagging allegiance to its wearer."};
descriptions["17156"]={cn:"想脱都脱不下来。",en:"This belt stays on, no matter what."};
descriptions["17157"]={cn:"记忆是智慧之母。",en:"Memory is the mother of all wisdom. Remember to buckle your belt."};
descriptions["17158"]={cn:"这根腰带很看好你，甚至到了崇拜的地步。",en:"This belt thinks very highly of you, almost to the point of worship."};
descriptions["17159"]={cn:"追随你参与每一场战斗。",en:"This belt will never threaten to leave you and, in fact, can not speak."};
descriptions["17160"]={cn:"一根永流传。",en:"This belt lasts as long as its owner."};
descriptions["17161"]={cn:"智慧能带来无穷的喜悦。",en:"Wisdom is the supreme part of happiness."};
descriptions["17162"]={cn:"谨以此腰带表彰你的贡献。",en:"This belt resists all your efforts."};
descriptions["17163"]={cn:"系上这根腰带，随时赶赴战场。",en:"This belt will always be ready whenever you need it."};
descriptions["17164"]={cn:"都给我绑起来！",en:"You\'ll be all tied up in the links of this belt."};
descriptions["17165"]={cn:"红花配绿叶，苍蝇叮烂肉。",en:"A man cannot learn wisdom by surrounding himself with ignorance."};
descriptions["17166"]={cn:"走雪地不打滑，走山路不摔跤。",en:"These boots are better at anticipating obstacles than your eyes."};
descriptions["17167"]={cn:"就是这么自信！",en:"These boots are just good boots, and it shows!"};
descriptions["17168"]={cn:"你悄悄地走了，不留下一丝声音。",en:"These boots let you walk through hostile terrain without making too much noise."};
descriptions["17169"]={cn:"头可断，血可流，造型不能丢。",en:"Always keep an open mind, a compassionate heart, and some seriously stylin\' boots."};
descriptions["17170"]={cn:"远离脚汗，告别脚臭，跟脚气说再见。",en:"These boots keep your feet dry."};
descriptions["17171"]={cn:"即便在最恶劣的环境里，仍会令人倍感舒适。",en:"These boots are very comfortable in hostile, off-road areas."};
descriptions["17172"]={cn:"不进水，广泛用于乘船旅行。",en:"These boots are frequently worn when traveling on big ships."};
descriptions["17173"]={cn:"千里之行，始于足下。",en:"The journey of a thousand miles begins with a single step."};
descriptions["17174"]={cn:"崇山峻岭，如履平地。",en:"These boots check the terrain before taking a step."};
descriptions["17175"]={cn:"能满足你的大部分需求。",en:"These boots are available to the most deserving."};
descriptions["17176"]={cn:"非常机智，避免你误入歧途。",en:"These boots are vigilant and will keep you from making a false step."};
descriptions["17177"]={cn:"千里之行，始于足下。",en:"The journey of a hundred miles begins with a single step."};
descriptions["17178"]={cn:"戴在你的手上显得愈发漂亮。",en:"This ring will be even more impressive on your finger."};
descriptions["17179"]={cn:"据说它有发射功能，你信么。",en:"It is said that this ring was once used as a projectile during a fight, bringing it to a quick end."};
descriptions["17180"]={cn:"小小指环，大大骄傲。",en:"A pretty ring that you can proudly wear on your finger."};
descriptions["17181"]={cn:"人不能两次戴上同一个指环...我是说，你可以带两个相同的指环，只是没必要...",en:"It\'s wise not to run in circles."};
descriptions["17182"]={cn:"使你和同伴们心意相连，可以在战场上辨明敌友。",en:"This ring lets you connect to your peers and distinguish your enemies."};
descriptions["17183"]={cn:"至尊戒，驭众戒。",en:"A ring that demands respect from your peers."};
descriptions["17184"]={cn:"让你的手指变得更好看。",en:"This ring will make your finger look quite a bit better."};
descriptions["17185"]={cn:"知己知彼，百战不殆。",en:"Knowing others is wisdom. Knowing yourself is enlightenment."};
descriptions["17186"]={cn:"惩恶扬善的必备道具。",en:"This ring is frequently worn during proceedings against Outlaws."};
descriptions["17187"]={cn:"献给最强的战士。",en:"This ring is reserved for only the best fighters."};
descriptions["17188"]={cn:"打架的时候，绝不会硌手。",en:"This ring won\'t get in your way while you go about your chores."};
descriptions["17189"]={cn:"完美的指环，一定能让你脑子开窍。",en:"Contemplate this perfectly infinite circle, that you may become infinitely wise."};
descriptions["17190"]={cn:"快刀斩乱麻。",en:"This sword removes everything in its path."};
descriptions["17191"]={cn:"所到之处，寸草不生。",en:"This sword will clear the battlefield in two or three movements."};
descriptions["17192"]={cn:"狭路相逢勇者胜！",en:"This sword doesn\'t deal in subtlety."};
descriptions["17193"]={cn:"令人印象深刻的武器，尤其是刺入你身体的时候。",en:"An impressive weapon, especially when it\'s thrust into your entrails."};
descriptions["17194"]={cn:"自由穿梭，击穿敌人。",en:"A weapon that can go all around, and through, your enemy."};
descriptions["17195"]={cn:"指哪儿不打哪儿！于是我用尽全力把它朝某人丢去。",en:"\"Shoot elsewhere, I tell you!\"... and I threw the staff with all my strength toward an unknown target."};
descriptions["17196"]={cn:"无论你是新人还是老战士，都请拿上这根魔杖。",en:"Whether you\'re a new recruit or a seasoned warrior, this wand is for you."};
descriptions["17197"]={cn:"高端大气上档次，残忍恐怖无节操。",en:"A rather majestic-looking wand with a cruel alter ego."};
descriptions["17198"]={cn:"华丽的外观，坚实的材质。",en:"It charms the enemy with its beauty, then suddenly shreds them."};
descriptions["17199"]={cn:"闪闪动人，刀刀见血。",en:"This sharpened ax has been coated in gold to be sure that each of its blows leaves it covered in blood."};
descriptions["17200"]={cn:"擅于把敌人大卸八块。",en:"This ax does a fine job of chopping your enemies into bite-sized pieces."};
descriptions["17201"]={cn:"它是噩梦的化身，三招内可置敌人死地。",en:"This ax is a nightmare for those on the wrong end of its blade, but it will only take three quick blows to put an end to their suffering."};
descriptions["17202"]={cn:"射程很远，直达天际。",en:"This bow has an enormous range; so far, in fact, that the projectiles can touch the sky."};
descriptions["17203"]={cn:"能轻而易举地从远处射中一只老鼠。",en:"With this bow, you\'ll be able to hit a fly from quite a long way away."};
descriptions["17204"]={cn:"无论是在战争时期还是和平时期，这把弓都令敌人闻风丧胆。",en:"A bow that\'s as terrifying during wartime as during peacetime."};
descriptions["17205"]={cn:"这把匕首会帮你兼顾前方和后方！可是谁保护它呢？",en:"This dagger will watch over your backside, as well as the front! But who watches it?"};
descriptions["17206"]={cn:"隐藏于暗处，杀人于无形。",en:"This dagger slips everywhere, whether it\'s into a pocket, or your enemy\'s lifeless corpse."};
descriptions["17207"]={cn:"手感好，造型好，谁用谁知道。",en:"This dagger is quite popular on the battlefield for its looks and handling."};
descriptions["17208"]={cn:"当你在战场上感到疲倦的时候，就在凯旋护盾上休息一下吧。",en:"Rest on this shield when you feel weary on the battlefield."};
descriptions["17209"]={cn:"不论是居家旅行还是杀人越货，它都能保障你的安全。",en:"A shield that guarantees protection in calm moments, but also in the most difficult moments."};
descriptions["17210"]={cn:"聪明人永远知道怎么保护自己。",en:"Wisdom will teach you to make use of your hands when need be."};
descriptions["17214"]={cn:"锻炼身体，铲除地下怪兽，造型别致，谁用谁知道。",en:"It moves us with its underground beats and gets us our exercise. Given its irregular curves, it\'s only beneficial for the one carrying it."};
descriptions["17217"]={cn:"一扇似乎在守护着伟大事物的庄严之门，离开的时候务必锁好。",en:"A magnificent door that seems to promise great things within. Make sure you lock it behind you."};
descriptions["17218"]={cn:"著名的 GvG 补丁。",en:"The famous GvG Patch!"};
descriptions["17220"]={cn:"经过武器大师精心提炼，可以制造出闪亮锋利的刀锋。",en:"Imperial Bauxite is highly sought-after by weapons masters thanks to its ability to make blades so shiny and smooth."};
descriptions["17221"]={cn:"传说这种水晶是由始祖龙的肉体分解而来。只是个传说。",en:"There\'s a legend that says that this mineral was created during the disembodiment of the World\'s dragons. But, y\'know, it\'s just a legend."};
descriptions["17222"]={cn:"9,000 枚硬币，因爱铸就。",en:"9,000 little Kamas, minted with love."};
descriptions["17223"]={cn:"9,800 枚硬币，因爱铸就。",en:"9,800 little Kamas, minted with love."};
descriptions["17225"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few grains should suffice."};
descriptions["17226"]={cn:"富人区里幸运猫的最爱。",en:"This fur has long been prized by the rich Ecaflips in the affluent quarters."};
descriptions["17227"]={cn:"据说福狸的尾巴掉了还能长出来，据说福狸总共有九条尾巴。",en:"A legend says that if a Lenald\'s tail is cut off, it can grow a new one, up to six times!"};
descriptions["17228"]={cn:"冬天戴上这对可爱的耳套能给你的耳朵保暖。",en:"These very cute muffs can be worn in winter to keep your Neals warm."};
descriptions["17229"]={cn:"懂得如何按照福狸的传统方式穿上这件衣服并系好带子是一项高超的技巧，需要耐心和熟练。",en:"Knowing how to fold and pleat the fabric around you in the traditional Lenald style is a skill that demands a lot of patience and dexterity."};
descriptions["17230"]={cn:"这双鞋非常舒适，走起路来就好像什么都没穿一样。",en:"These shoes are particularly comfy; walking feels very natural, as if you weren\'t wearing anything."};
descriptions["17231"]={cn:"适合固定任何衣服，这样你才不会衣衫不整。",en:"This belt allows you to keep any garment in place so that it doesn\'t constantly shift."};
descriptions["17232"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["17233"]={cn:"只要试穿过就会知道有多么舒适，完全不想脱下来。",en:"Once you\'ve tried on this cloak and felt how comfortable it is, you\'ll want to wear it forever. Taking it off would just be illogical."};
descriptions["17234"]={cn:"福狸毛皮制成的地毯，能为任何地面平添奢华风度。",en:"This rug, created from Lenald fur, will add a nice touch of luxury to any interior."};
descriptions["17235"]={cn:"并不来自西方，只是四方和西瓜的合体，小心轻坐。",en:"Better not sit down too hard; there\'s a risk you\'ll smash it all to pieces."};
descriptions["17236"]={cn:"处处体现着福狸武术的精妙，只是问题在于你用不用得来。",en:"Made according to the pure Lenald Maltial Alt tradition. The only thing left is to see how well you can handle it."};
descriptions["17237"]={cn:"这件道服已经穿了十几年，看上去非常破旧。但它仍然跟以前一样拥有优良的品质。",en:"This kimono was worn for more than a decade; it\'s pretty beat up, but still has all the other characteristics it did so long ago."};
descriptions["17238"]={cn:"遇到伏兵的时候，临时充当头盔还是不错的。当然，最大的用处还是烧饭，如果有火的话。",en:"Practical as a makeshift helmet in case of ambush, but mostly useful for cooking a good meal or two wherever you go, assuming there\'s fire."};
descriptions["17239"]={cn:"富人区里幸运猫和宝藏猎人的最爱。",en:"This fur has long been prized by the rich Ecaflips in the affluent quarters and by the greediest Enutrofs."};
descriptions["17240"]={cn:"福狸间流传着这样的谚语：自慧子素于冷静的伦。",en:"A wise old Lenald once said: \"Wisdom only comes to those who lemain tlanquil.\""};
descriptions["17241"]={cn:"阳光照射强烈的时候，帽子里会飘出一股臭气。但是无论如何这顶帽子都很酷。",en:"It\'s true that, when the sun is very strong, a slight odor of dried meat wafts from the hat, but that doesn\'t change how fabulous you look wearing it."};
descriptions["17242"]={cn:"福狸小朋友们从小就会做胜利手势，这个护符相当于胜利手势专业资格鉴定证书。",en:"In childhood, Lenald children learn to make the sign of Victoly, and this amulet is a testament to their gesturing expertise."};
descriptions["17243"]={cn:"顶部带有厚厚的毛，削铁如泥大概是不可能的。",en:"With the thick fur on their tops, no one will expect the unquestionable cutting power of these cards."};
descriptions["17244"]={cn:"正如福狸王闪耀的智慧一般，这胸甲能闪瞎你。",en:"As brilliant as the Empelol himself, the breastplate hurts your eyes a little."};
descriptions["17245"]={cn:"好好学学福狸的鬼伎俩吧，看看他们是怎么把毒藏在戒指里的。（佐以砂糖，口味尤佳）",en:"You\'ve gotta know how to be sneaky like a Lenald and hide the poison in this ring. (It\'s even better if you\'ve added sugar.)"};
descriptions["17246"]={cn:"老福狸都知道好好保护颈椎，老了之后才不会生病。",en:"An old Lenald needs to know when to cover his neck so he doesn\'t become sick as a dog."};
descriptions["17247"]={cn:"只要你用这件披风把自己包得严严实实，乌鸦就不会来偷你的奶酪了。",en:"When you\'re well camouflaged underneath this cloak, the Crobaks won\'t come to steal your cheese."};
descriptions["17248"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["17249"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few grains should suffice."};
descriptions["17250"]={cn:"柔软的毛皮。使你在冰窟里保持温暖。",en:"A soft fur. A very soft fur, in fact, that will keep you warm in your burrow."};
descriptions["17251"]={cn:"带有一种特殊的由胡萝卜素调和而成的颜色。",en:"This fabric is a magnificent explosion of cawotene-red color!"};
descriptions["17252"]={cn:"耳朵那里磨损得特别厉害。",en:"This bandana, a sign of perserverence, is worn tightly knotted around the ears."};
descriptions["17253"]={cn:"小常识：黑疯兔只在放假的时候才会换底裤。",en:"Little-known fact: Black Wabbits only change their underwear on holidays."};
descriptions["17254"]={cn:"有人说黑疯兔脚也能带来幸运，你真的相信么？",en:"It would seem that Black Wabbit Paws bring luck. But Black Wabbits don\'t carry them; they see lucky charms as a sign of weakness."};
descriptions["17255"]={cn:"权力的象征，只有佩戴者才能安全地进入黑疯兔的地盘。",en:"This amulet serves as a sign of authorization, allowing safe passage through certain areas of Black Wabbit occupied territory."};
descriptions["17256"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["17257"]={cn:"这盾一点儿都不欢乐。或许你应该找更高级更欢乐的盾换上？",en:"This shield is a bit of a killjoy, frankly. Maybe you could try a high-level joy-revival treatment over at the armorer\'s place?"};
descriptions["17258"]={cn:"看起来不太像匕首，不过从你后面插进去的时候真的很带感哦。",en:"It may not look like much, but it really hurts when it\'s planted in your behind."};
descriptions["17259"]={cn:"福狸把宿敌的形象印在头巾上，时时激励自己去复仇。",en:"The mark of the Lenalds\' sworn enemies is on this headband - just to provoke them."};
descriptions["17260"]={cn:"戴上之后，你会变得比输给龟龟的疯兔还笨。",en:"This ring will make you as nuts as a Black Wabbit at full steam."};
descriptions["17261"]={cn:"以柔软著称，你穿上让朋友感受一下。",en:"The Black Coat is prized for its solidity, exotic aroma, and strength of character."};
descriptions["17262"]={cn:"喜欢张大嘴巴伊欧普人的要注意了，别被自己的肩膀弄得下巴脱臼。",en:"Slack-jawed Iops must pay close attention if they don\'t want to dislocate their jaw with a blow from their own shoulder."};
descriptions["17263"]={cn:"贴身设计，符合你肩膀的曲线，为战斗带来舒适感。不但能使穿戴者免受伤害，还能放松你的颈部。",en:"These pompoms, affixed to your shoulders, will be a boon in times of war. Not only do they protect the wearer from blows received, but they relax your neck as well."};
descriptions["17264"]={cn:"内含神秘能量，激发接触者暴躁的本性，赋予他们力量。",en:"A mysterious energy that gives blind courage and strength to whoever comes in contact with it."};
descriptions["17265"]={cn:"戴上这枚戒指，你感觉怒不可遏。",en:"Like watching Hunee Bow Meow, putting this ring on your finger provokes insatiable rage."};
descriptions["17266"]={cn:"神秘的能量饮料，已经使很多人变蠢。",en:"A mysteriously energizing drink that\'s turned more than one person nuts - or simply made them idiots."};
descriptions["17267"]={cn:"给真正的黑疯兔！",en:"For real Black Wabbits!"};
descriptions["17268"]={cn:"这把权杖充满愤怒渴望复仇。它曾为一个杀死毕尔的愤怒新娘所有。",en:"This scepter is marked by rage and thirst for revenge. It used to belong to Beatwix Kiddo."};
descriptions["17269"]={cn:"这鞋子怎么说呢，至少爆炸发生的时候能让你逃快点。",en:"These shoes, extensively tested by Awnie the Emiw, will let you run faster than a bomb explosion!"};
descriptions["17270"]={cn:"护符在此，坏人统统不要过来！",en:"Protects you from those with bad intentions, especially those who want to directly harm you."};
descriptions["17271"]={cn:"这件胸甲是用兔毛做的，除了保暖和护身外，还能帮你存储吃饭时掉落的胡萝卜屑。",en:"This breastplate is made from beard hair. It will protect your torso from explosion damage, and it\'ll also store Cawwot crumbs for later."};
descriptions["17272"]={cn:"多少年过去了，黑疯兔家族依然念念不忘祖先当年愚蠢的自我牺牲行为。",en:"It has been passed down through generations of Black Wabbit families to honor and remember the stupid sacrifice of their ancestors."};
descriptions["17273"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["17275"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few grains should suffice."};
descriptions["17276"]={cn:"柔软的毛皮。使你在冰窟里保持温暖。",en:"A soft fur. A very soft fur, in fact, that will keep you warm in your burrow."};
descriptions["17277"]={cn:"百分百自然的色彩。",en:"This dye lets you give a discreet and 100% natural color to all your Wabbit fur garments."};
descriptions["17278"]={cn:"小白兔白又白，戴上面具跑起来。",en:"You shouldn\'t follow strange white Wabbits who run like madmen into dark holes..."};
descriptions["17279"]={cn:"以柔软著称，你穿上感受一下。",en:"The Wabbit Coat is prized for its softness, suppleness, and strength of character."};
descriptions["17280"]={cn:"有人说疯兔脚能带来幸运，你想过福狸的感受么？",en:"It would seem that Wabbit Paws bring luck. But Wabbits generally prefer Lenald paws as lucky charms..."};
descriptions["17281"]={cn:"签署文件是一项特殊待遇，所有的长耳都...\n这东西就是用来盖章的！所以人们才叫它印戒！",en:"Signing scrolls is a special treat, in the noble court where the long-ears meet... It\'s fow stampin\'! That\'s why they call it a Stampew!"};
descriptions["17282"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["17283"]={cn:"小巧可爱，但是锋利无边！",en:"This cute little axe has not lost its edge, and it can fix a sore throat very quickly."};
descriptions["17284"]={cn:"如何诱惑你的敌人？只要在面前插上胡萝卜引诱敌人就好了。",en:"How best to lure your adversary? Just stick a Cawwot under their nose and they\'ll come running!"};
descriptions["17285"]={cn:"像兔粑粑的身材一样宽。",en:"This amulet is as wide as a Wo Wabbit on a diet!"};
descriptions["17286"]={cn:"喜欢吃胡萝卜的人都爱它，它能让胡萝卜始终清脆爽口。",en:"The bag pwefewwed by anyone who loves eating Cawwots. It keeps them fwesh and cwunchy the whole day."};
descriptions["17287"]={cn:"看起来不太像匕首，不过从你后面插进去的时候真的很带感哦。",en:"It may not look like much, but it really hurts when it\'s planted in your behind."};
descriptions["17288"]={cn:"据说咬过它的疯兔牙都碎了。",en:"Those that tried to eat it broke their teeth!"};
descriptions["17289"]={cn:"心情好，一整天。",en:"A Pompom tail that\'s been primped and prettified all day."};
descriptions["17290"]={cn:"蓬松柔软的腰带。寄上扣子，你觉得舒适极了。",en:"This belt has been pampered its entire life. As soon as the buckle was in place, it knew it was the prettiest."};
descriptions["17291"]={cn:"蓬松的大盾，完美吸收攻击。",en:"Cushions blows in case of falls and bounces."};
descriptions["17292"]={cn:"啃了它还是吞了它，随你便。重要的是，有足够的胡萝卜指环给你吃。",en:"Whether you nibble \'em or swallow \'em whole doesn\'t matter; the only thing that does is that there are more Cawwot Wounds to eat after."};
descriptions["17293"]={cn:"要站在兔长官的地位上看待问题。",en:"You up to being the Gwand Viziew in place of the Gwand Viziew?"};
descriptions["17294"]={cn:"既能抵挡攻击，又能抵挡杀虫剂。",en:"This cloak protects its wearer against bad spells and pesticides."};
descriptions["17295"]={cn:"这件胸甲是用兔毛做的，除了保暖和护身外，还能帮你存储吃饭时掉落的胡萝卜屑。",en:"This breastplate is made from beard hair. It will protect your torso from various projectiles, and it\'ll also store Cawwot crumbs for later."};
descriptions["17296"]={cn:"让你跑得比一般的疯兔还快，前提是前面要有胡萝卜引诱你。",en:"These sandals will let you run faster than a Wabbit runs after a Cawwot, and that\'s already pretty fast."};
descriptions["17297"]={cn:"蕴含魔力，也许正是兔长官的能量源泉。",en:"A magic aura comes from this amulet. Maybe this is where the Gwand Viziew got his power of persuasion?"};
descriptions["17298"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["17300"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few grains should suffice."};
descriptions["17301"]={cn:"长期浸泡于胡萝卜汁中，颜色鲜亮。",en:"This fabric was dyed with Cawwot juice to give it that lively color."};
descriptions["17302"]={cn:"用于制造机械兔的一种神秘金属，高强度超耐磨。唯一的缺点是很难焊接。",en:"Midalurgee metal is frequently used in the production of Wobots. It\'s light, resistant, but incredibly difficult to weld."};
descriptions["17303"]={cn:"保护你在摔跤时免受脑震荡。",en:"Pwotect youw skull fwom stwong impacts and landslides."};
descriptions["17304"]={cn:"如疯兔般轻盈！",en:"It will allow you to make an impwovised sheltew undewgwound."};
descriptions["17305"]={cn:"至少能帮你把头撑在脖子上。",en:"To help keep your head on your shoulders, where it belongs."};
descriptions["17306"]={cn:"穿上这个你就不用裸体了。",en:"With this on, you won\'t be naked!"};
descriptions["17307"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["17308"]={cn:"有史以来，凡是穿着橙色皇袍的疯兔战士对阵福狸时至今未尝败绩！",en:"FACT: no warrior who wears the Oranged Wa into battle will ever fall before a Lenald!"};
descriptions["17309"]={cn:"瞄准了打！",en:"Aim straight between the two prongs."};
descriptions["17310"]={cn:"给你从头到脖子的保护，身体的剩余部分你自己负责。",en:"Head to neck protection! You\'re on your own for the other parts."};
descriptions["17311"]={cn:"这副手套能避免你收割胡萝卜的时候弄脏手。",en:"It will let you avoid getting your hands dirty while harvesting Cawwots."};
descriptions["17312"]={cn:"不管你有没有真本事，只要扛着这吓人的兵器上街，福狸们一见到就四散逃跑了。",en:"No need to train too much; when you take this out, the Lenalds can\'t help but run away!"};
descriptions["17313"]={cn:"只用最上乘材料精心装饰。",en:"This belt is adorned with only the best hardware."};
descriptions["17314"]={cn:"自从疯兔们发明了长矛抓鱼法之后，就再也没有疯兔用胡萝卜钓鱼了。",en:"One day, the Wabbits had an idea: why not fish for Loot with a spear? It was a fantastic idea! Now they can have fish with their Cawwots."};
descriptions["17315"]={cn:"非常危险的兵器，连拿着它的人都会有被敲碎的风险。",en:"This club is very dangerous, even for the one carrying it. You should keep your distance so you don\'t crush your tender parts."};
descriptions["17316"]={cn:"上赞仓前把则总天然颜料涂在脸丧，绝对费给你带来好运。",en:"Put this waw paint on youw face befowe heading out to battle - it\'ll bwing luck to the lucky."};
descriptions["17317"]={cn:"这块大盾能很好地保护你，当然你也看不到外面的东西了。",en:"This immense shield protects you well, sure, but you can\'t see anything over it."};
descriptions["17318"]={cn:"看这做工很明显是车间里临时工的作品，弱爆了。奇怪的是东西用起来其实还挺不错的。",en:"This ring is a mess of amateur mechanics! Nothing is the way it should be, but strangely, it works pretty well."};
descriptions["17319"]={cn:"不，不会发出X射线。不，也不会给你超能力。别再问啦！爱买买，不买滚。",en:"No, these glasses aren\'t x-ray. And no, they don\'t give you superpowers like shooting lasers out of your eyes. They are super classy though!"};
descriptions["17320"]={cn:"其实是把机关钥匙。插进去，拧一拧，机械兔就会动起来了。",en:"This medal is used like a little key. It\'s inserted into the Wobot to turn (and keep) it on."};
descriptions["17321"]={cn:"备用底裤，以防发生意外情况。",en:"In case of sudden terrors, you\'ll be thankful to have a back-up plan."};
descriptions["17322"]={cn:"想穿着这双靴子走路可要费点功夫，它们非常重。不过某种程度上，它们还是能帮助你移动的。",en:"You\'ll have to train pretty seriously to even be able to walk a step in these boots. They\'re really heavy, but somehow they still help you move more easily."};
descriptions["17323"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["17324"]={cn:"看起来很可爱，你想一口吞了。可是上面的兔毛总是让你恶心。",en:"This fine tuft of hair has been imbued with the delicate and sweet odor of cawwot. It almost makes you want to eat it - but then you\'d have hair on your tongue."};
descriptions["17325"]={cn:"制定法律，盖上印章，在兔皇面前显摆！",en:"Affix your seal, impose your laws, and pose in front of the Wa!"};
descriptions["17326"]={cn:"柔软结实的靠垫，兔皇帝也无可挑剔。你也肯定挑不出什么毛病。",en:"This stuffed Cwown is soft and cushy enough for the Wa\'s behind, so it should be more than enough for yours."};
descriptions["17327"]={cn:"珍贵的皇室传家宝，世世代代被守卫严加看管。随后，复制品问世，被出价最高的竞价者买走了。",en:"A precious heirloom guarded fiercely by generations of royal Wabbits. Then it was copied and the copies were sold off to the highest bidders."};
descriptions["17328"]={cn:"疯兔们称这是他们伟大的皇帝兔生中的第一把权杖，他很小时候就有了，后来又把它遗忘在一堆装备中了。",en:"The Wabbits say that it\'s the first scepter ever received by their Wa, during his childhood, but he forgot it among all his possessions."};
descriptions["17329"]={cn:"为了能让身材更加苗条诱惑，兔皇帝毫不犹豫地穿上了束腹带。不过，穿它的感觉那是相当痛苦。",en:"In order to quickly look very svelte and seductive, the Wa doesn\'t hesitate to reach for his corset. In any case, it\'s pretty painful to wear."};
descriptions["17330"]={cn:"这对可充气臂环使上臂看起来肌肉发达又强壮，可以把拜拜肉全都藏起来。",en:"These inflatable armbands surround the arm so that it looks strong and well-muscled, when in reality, it\'s hiding a ton of flab."};
descriptions["17331"]={cn:"可以瘦身用，参见兔皇帝的身材！",en:"This cloak is very slimming. Just look at the Wa\'s figure!"};
descriptions["17332"]={cn:"传说中兔皇帝的权力象征！终于到你手上了！你恨不得马上戴上它耀武扬威，对吧？别掩饰了。",en:"The legendary Wa Wabbit\'s Cwown! Finally in your clutches! You know you were hoping to try it on at least once in your life as an adventurer, don\'t pretend you weren\'t."};
descriptions["17333"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["17335"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky, putrid substance contained in this flask! A few grains should suffice."};
descriptions["17336"]={cn:"你得十分小心才能加工这种毛皮，你可能受感染。",en:"Take care when handling this fur; it can contaminate you."};
descriptions["17337"]={cn:"僵尸兔就算没有牙齿也会来咬你。",en:"Even without their teeth, the Zwombbits still try to bite you!"};
descriptions["17338"]={cn:"虽然不太结实，但是它能轻松在别人身上开洞刮骨。",en:"Although fragile, they can easily make a new hole in someone\'s torso and cut them to the bone."};
descriptions["17339"]={cn:"僵尸兔脚上根本没有皮，它们好像并不介意，不过没皮怎么行。",en:"There\'s no skin left on the Zwombbit paws. They\'re not very appealing, but they\'re certainly useful."};
descriptions["17340"]={cn:"离这爪子太近可不是什么好事。只要被它划伤一下，你就要送去隔离了。",en:"This claw coming near you is not a happy thought. Even one injury caused by it and you\'re sure to be quarantined."};
descriptions["17341"]={cn:"衣服破破烂烂还沾满了恶心的毛，但是你还是想穿上。因为它能在战场上让你金刚不破。",en:"This torso is putrid and covered in filthy hairs, but that doesn\'t stop you from wearing it because it assures unparalleled close-combat protection."};
descriptions["17342"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["17343"]={cn:"你要是觉得戴上这个面具会让你变丑，请先自己照照镜子。",en:"If you think this mask will make you too ugly, go look in a mirror first; it\'ll put things in perspective for you."};
descriptions["17344"]={cn:"虽然背包感染了病毒，破败不堪，但是能保持里面东西干净完好。",en:"This putrid sack can still keep things clean."};
descriptions["17345"]={cn:"胡萝卜已被病毒感染，它现在无坚不摧！是名符其实的大规模杀伤性武器！",en:"This Cawwot was infected by the Viwus, and now it\'s rigid and unbreakable! It\'s a veritable weapon of mass destruction!"};
descriptions["17346"]={cn:"为了避免被病毒感染，你必须知道如何保护自己，而且不要接近僵尸兔。",en:"To avoid Viwus contamination, you need to know how to protect yourself and avoid getting too close to Zwombbits."};
descriptions["17347"]={cn:"我们可没出老千，你不过是运气烂罢了。",en:"We\'we not cheating you - you just have wotten luck."};
descriptions["17348"]={cn:"这件披风由零零星星的烂皮制成，穿上它就好像背着块肉到处跑！让你看起来像只母咕咕！",en:"This cloak was made from several bits and pieces of skin. It\'s like a piece of meat you carry around! You can be just like Brrrbley Spears!"};
descriptions["17349"]={cn:"也许这就是病毒扩散的源头？",en:"Could it be the origin of the widespread infection in the burrows?"};
descriptions["17350"]={cn:"从僵尸兔的脖子上切下三角形肉块的理想选择。现在你明白为什么有些兔肉的形状符合几何学原理了！",en:"Perfect for cutting triangles out of Zwombbit necks (which will allow you to complete your collection of geometrically shaped Zwombbit flesh)!"};
descriptions["17351"]={cn:"如果你想在僵尸兔成群出没的隧道里活命，就必须把这东西喝下去。",en:"If you think you can survive in the Zwombbit-infested tunnels, you\'ve not yet had a swig of this drink."};
descriptions["17352"]={cn:"箭上有毒！一旦被射中就死定了！",en:"The arrows spread the infection. Once hit by one, there\'s no escaping!"};
descriptions["17353"]={cn:"这个戒指跟病毒有千丝万缕的联系，能使携带者免疫感染。",en:"This ring was in direct contact with the Viwus, which makes its wearer immune to the menace."};
descriptions["17354"]={cn:"分子级别的改良使得这件披风轻盈无比，同时又极其坚韧。",en:"This cloak was submitted to numerous molecular modifications, which improved the material\'s resistance and greatly increased its abilities."};
descriptions["17355"]={cn:"经常穿戴有助于改善你的基因。",en:"This belt might modify your genetic code if you wear it too often."};
descriptions["17356"]={cn:"采用最新生物技术制成的新款战斗装备，性能大大超越任何用传统工艺制作的装备。",en:"Particle reinforcement allows an auto-regenerating material to be joined to a removable one, making movement one millisecond faster."};
descriptions["17357"]={cn:"先进的工艺制品，其轻便性让你的行动如行云流水。不过一旦受到伤害，却会造成深深的刺痛。",en:"Your movements will be fluid, giving you incomparable combat abilities. But any damage sustained will cause pain that stabs through you like a lance."};
