descriptions["17365"]={cn:"手工雕刻木质胡萝卜龙蛋，疯兔岛龙蛋的完美复制品。",en:"This Cawwot Dofus, carved from noble wood, is a perfect copy of the Dofus from the Wabbit Islands."};
descriptions["17367"]={cn:"说明：沿着格子自动播种（成功率 50%）。",en:"The Sow-n-Sow automatically plants a seed (50%) on an adjacent cell every 4 minutes."};
descriptions["17368"]={cn:"小小的一粒种子，带给你大大的幸福，还是黑颜色的。",en:"A small Black Cawwot seed, which is guaranteed to grow beautiful Cawwots - black ones, of course."};
descriptions["17369"]={cn:"排好队型，先上砧板，再一起下锅。",en:"This Black Cawwot is just waiting to be thrown in the reserves, or the kitchen."};
descriptions["17374"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few drops should suffice."};
descriptions["17375"]={cn:"你可以利用这种碎片把自己伪装成被洗脑的黑疯兔。\n收集三片碎片可制成一件衣服。",en:"This bit of tunic will allow you to make an Indoctrinated Black Wabbit disguise.\nCollect 3 pieces to make the costume."};
descriptions["17376"]={cn:"穿上这件完美的伪装，你就能溜进工地。",en:"This costume, which to you looks perfect, will allow you to sneak into the construction site."};
descriptions["17377"]={cn:"出于众所周知的原因，毛巾家族历来不能去游泳。",en:"You know what\'s sad? Towels never get to go swimming!"};
descriptions["17378"]={cn:"毛巾毛巾我们去游泳吧？",en:"Going swimmin\'? Don\'t forget to bring a towel!"};
descriptions["17379"]={cn:"毛巾毛巾我们去游泳吧？",en:"Going swimmin\'? Don\'t forget to bring a towel!"};
descriptions["17380"]={cn:"邀几个海滩边的漂亮姑娘一起野炊，吃完后一起躲进边上的帐篷里...嘿，谁把灯关了？！",en:"You know what this means... Yep, set up the tent and invite the girls round, because it\'s sleepover night!"};
descriptions["17381"]={cn:"待客必备，值得拥有！",en:"A must-have for photos that\'ll make your friends jelly!"};
descriptions["17382"]={cn:"啊！有人偷窥！是约翰！",en:"It\'s never been easier to slip into your bathing costume far from prying eyes."};
