descriptions["17424"]={cn:"添放到庇护袋的制作室或庇护领地里，你可以使用此设备进行 0 到 150 的畜牧作业。",en:"Add this to the Crafting Room of your Haven Bag or to your Haven World to make level 0 to 150 recipes for the Trapper profession."};
descriptions["17427"]={cn:"长枪一定是使用过很多次了，枪头非常钝，这种状态肯定不能用。",en:"This lance must have been used a lot, because its tip is incredibly blunt; it\'s unusable in this state."};
descriptions["17428"]={cn:"头盔散发出烂胡萝卜和烧焦的味道。如果我是你，就把头转到一边去。",en:"This helmet smells like charred stuff and rotten Cawwot. I\'d avoid putting it on my head if I were you."};
descriptions["17429"]={cn:"一套护甲完好地收藏在箱子里。但是箱子太旧了，锁已经生锈，没办法打开。",en:"A set of armor put away quite nicely in its case. But the case is so old the lock must have rusted, because it\'s impossible to open."};
descriptions["17430"]={cn:"魔法加持的胡萝卜汁，没人知道喝了会出现什么副作用。",en:"A Cawwot juice with magic properties. Unfortunately, noone knows what the side effects are."};
descriptions["17431"]={cn:"疯兔出品。这双靴子浸渍着胡萝卜汁，根据代代相传的秘密配方制成。",en:"Boots made by Wabbits. They\'re imbued with magic cawwot juice made from a secret recipe handed down through generations."};
descriptions["17432"]={cn:"这副肩甲浸渍着胡萝卜汁，根据代代相传的秘密配方制成。",en:"They\'re imbued with magic cawwot juice made from a secret recipe handed down through generations."};
descriptions["17433"]={cn:"疯兔出品。这副胸甲浸渍着胡萝卜汁，根据代代相传的秘密配方制成。",en:"A breastplate proudly made by Wabbits. It\'s imbued with magic cawwot juice made from a secret recipe handed down through generations."};
descriptions["17434"]={cn:"知道这意味着什么吧？对啦，你是公会的人啦！",en:"You know what this costume means, don\'t you? That\'s right! It means you belong to a guild."};
descriptions["17436"]={cn:"穿着它，你就跟黑疯兔没什么两样了。",en:"And away we go! This ravishing Black Wabbit costume will look stunning on you. We\'d almost think you were really one of them."};
descriptions["17437"]={cn:"你已经掌握了水宗的功夫。",en:"Your training is finished; you\'re adept at the ancestral water arts!"};
descriptions["17438"]={cn:"你已经掌握了火宗的功夫。",en:"Your training is finished; you\'re adept at the ancestral fire arts!"};
descriptions["17439"]={cn:"象征着曾经作为岛屿占有者的疯兔。",en:"This old boulder used to symbolize the Wabbits\' ownership of the islands."};
descriptions["17441"]={cn:"小心，里面也许藏着胡萝卜炸弹...",en:"Be very cautious - there might be a Cawwot Bomb hidden in the stuffing..."};
descriptions["17442"]={cn:"福狸跟疯兔说：我们得坐下来好好谈谈。",en:"The Lenald said to the Wabbit: \'The time has come to talk of many things...\'"};
descriptions["17443"]={cn:"福狸地毯特别版。要把福狸毛皮在太阳晒很长时间才能变成这样的白色。",en:"This rug is a variant of the Lenald Lug. The fur was left in the sun for a much longer time to obtain a paler color."};
descriptions["17444"]={cn:"象征着福狸王的信使。",en:"This statue represents the Lenald Empelol\'s messenger."};
descriptions["17445"]={cn:"便携的福狸便当。由黑胡萝卜、鱼以及香米制成。",en:"This Lenald Bento is a lunch that\'s easy to tlanspolt. It\'s tladitionally plepaled with Black Cawwots, fish, and a few glains of Vanilla Lice."};
descriptions["17446"]={cn:"不含玫瑰...",en:"A refreshing rose drink (note: does not contain actual roses)."};
descriptions["17447"]={cn:"拼装一只机械兔需要好多这样的部件，别弄丢了。",en:"This piece is necessary for the construction of a series of Wobots. Guard it closely; there are only so many."};
descriptions["17450"]={cn:"记载了全部地点，或者说大部分地点。所有通往秘密胡萝卜储藏室的入口都已清晰标明！",en:"Everything\'s there - well, almost. All the entrances to the burrows are marked and indicated on the map, all the way to the secret Cawwot stash!"};
descriptions["17451"]={cn:"表嘛，窝表起来！",en:"A cozy little bed for snuggling up warm and comfy, just like the burrow."};
descriptions["17452"]={cn:"把胡萝卜都藏在后面，别让疯兔看见。",en:"Now you can contemplate your Cawwots tranquilly, hidden from view!"};
descriptions["17453"]={cn:"漂亮又好用，不时飘出一股疯兔炖菜的味道。也许里面住着疯兔一家...",en:"This beautiful wardrobe is not only deep and practical, it gives off a nice scent of stew that the others don\'t have."};
descriptions["17454"]={cn:"胖嘟嘟的，忍不住要抱抱。",en:"The Wo Wabbit Toy is so huge and cuddly that you feel a strong urge to hug it."};
descriptions["17455"]={cn:"用胡萝卜调戏它！",en:"It\'s so cute when it tries to catch the Cawwot on a stick that you definitely shouldn\'t give it to him."};
descriptions["17456"]={cn:"经由特殊树脂加固，表面通了几个洞透光。你还能闻到一股疯兔炖菜的气味。",en:"This Cawwot has been hardened with a special resin and several holes have been punched through it to let a candle\'s light shine through. A nice odor of stew is coming from it."};
descriptions["17457"]={cn:"睿智的皇帝都明白睡觉也是工作的一部分。",en:"A wise Wa knows lying in bed is an essential part of the job."};
descriptions["17458"]={cn:"胡萝卜状的把手。务必好好照料，以免被疯兔咬坏。",en:"The handles are in the shape of Cawwots. You\'ll have to take good care of it so it doesn\'t become garden compost."};
descriptions["17459"]={cn:"巨大的胡萝卜，人们不得不把它剁成一张桌子，这样大家都可以欣赏它...",en:"This Cawwot was so huge they decided to chop it up into a table so they could always look at it and enjoy it."};
descriptions["17460"]={cn:"胡萝卜圆凳的改良版，以适应你弯曲的后背。如果你真要坐上去，请找个木匠加固。",en:"Since you got this stool, its design has been upgraded to better fit your curvaceous behind. If you plan on sitting on it anytime soon, visit the appropriate workshop and follow the recipe to make the latest adjustments."};
descriptions["17461"]={cn:"你的宠物到底多喜欢胡萝卜，以至于把所有东西都咬烂？",en:"Could it be that your pet is so addicted to Cawwots that it\'s going to tear everything apart?"};
descriptions["17462"]={cn:"疯兔家里都会放一个来膜拜。而在福狸家里只会看到撕烂的兔皇帝公仔。",en:"The Wa Wabbit Stuffed Toy is as admired as the Wa Wabbit is among the Wabbits. In Lenald homes, you\'ll only find shredded ones..."};
descriptions["17463"]={cn:"疯兔回答福狸：不谈不谈我不谈，麻麻没回来。",en:"The Wabbit responded to the Lenald: \'But wait a bit before we have our chat. For I\'m out of breath, and a little fat.\'"};
descriptions["17464"]={cn:"组装属于你自己的机械兔吧！",en:"Assembly instructions have been included, just in case the toy ends up in a million pieces."};
descriptions["17465"]={cn:"里面种了太多胡萝卜，冒出来的只有胡萝卜茎。",en:"Too many Cawwots have been planted in the planter, which leave space for only the stalks to appear."};
descriptions["17466"]={cn:"曾经只是家里的一个祈福祭坛，祈祷来年好收成。",en:"This lawge Totem used to be a prayer altar in the middle of a huge farm."};
descriptions["17467"]={cn:"曾经只是家里的一个祈福祭坛，祈祷来年好收成。",en:"This Little Totem used to be a prayer altar in a home, where prayers would be made for a good harvest."};
descriptions["17468"]={cn:"随时可以搬进厨房的胡萝卜。",en:"A huge pile of Cawwots just waiting to be taken to the reserves or to the kitchen."};
descriptions["17469"]={cn:"精挑细选的新鲜有机胡萝卜，欢迎品尝。",en:"Some well-chosen, fresh, organic Cawwots. Enjoy."};
descriptions["17470"]={cn:"看起来能吃，其实确实是木质的。",en:"This giant Cawwot is made entirely of wood; the realism is impressive, is it not?"};
descriptions["17471"]={cn:"看起来能吃，其实确实是木质的。喂，别咬了！牙齿还要不要了？",en:"This giant Cawwot is made entirely of wood; the realism is impressive, is it not? So impressive that someone has already tried to eat it."};
descriptions["17472"]={cn:"如果你想保护自己的土地，这块砖墙能完美地抵挡住福狸。",en:"If you want to wall off your land, this wall is perfect for sending the Lenalds into fits of rage."};
descriptions["17473"]={cn:"如果你想保护自己的土地，这块砖墙能完美地抵挡住福狸的攻击。即便福狸撞掉一只耳朵，也无法冲破防御。",en:"If you want to wall off your land, this large wall is perfect for sending the Lenalds into fits of rage. They\'ve even already broken off an ear!"};
descriptions["17474"]={cn:"如果你想保护自己的土地，这块砖墙能完美地抵挡住福狸。",en:"If you want to wall off your land, this lawge wall is perfect for sending the Lenalds into fits of rage."};
descriptions["17475"]={cn:"如果你想保护自己的土地，这块砖墙能完美地抵挡住福狸的攻击。即便福狸撞掉一只耳朵，也无法冲破防御。",en:"If you want to wall off your land, this wall is perfect for sending the Lenalds into fits of rage. They\'ve even already broken off an ear!"};
descriptions["17478"]={cn:"编了号的胡萝卜汤罐，但愿没人忘记里面是哪种萝卜...",en:"This substance was numbered so as not to forget... erm... What sort of Cawwots went into this again?"};
descriptions["17479"]={cn:"最好别打开，里面的东西感觉不太对劲。",en:"Maybe you should just leave this one sealed. The substance inside looks a little suspect."};
descriptions["17480"]={cn:"一罐胡萝卜汤。也许只是种子汤。",en:"A fruity substance in a tube. Maybe it\'s an essence in the making?"};
descriptions["17481"]={cn:"这个模型从某个角度证明了罗霉罗的伪科学。",en:"This sculpture illustrates, in a way that only it could, the extent of Dr. Womewo\'s quackery."};
descriptions["17482"]={cn:"看起来能吃，其实确实是木质的。",en:"This giant Cawwot is made entirely of wood; the realism is impressive, is it not?"};
descriptions["17483"]={cn:"看起来能吃，其实确实是木质的。喂，别咬了！牙齿还要不要了？",en:"This giant Cawwot is made entirely of wood; the realism is impressive, is it not? So impressive that someone has already tried to eat it."};
descriptions["17484"]={cn:"随时可以搬进厨房的黑胡萝卜。",en:"A huge pile of Black Cawwots just waiting to be taken to the reserves or to the kitchen."};
descriptions["17485"]={cn:"精挑细选的新鲜有机黑胡萝卜，欢迎品尝。",en:"Some well-chosen, fresh, organic Black Cawwots. Enjoy."};
descriptions["17486"]={cn:"如果你想保护自己的土地，这块砖墙是完美的选择。",en:"If you want to wall off your land, this little wall is perfect."};
descriptions["17487"]={cn:"它能运很多很多多汁的胡萝卜！",en:"This chariot allows you to haul an incredible number of juicy Cawwots!"};
descriptions["17488"]={cn:"在被福狸永久借走之前，它曾属于疯兔...一头很锋利，另一头更锋利。简直是致命武器。",en:"It used to belong to the Wabbits before it was permanently \"borrowed\" by the Lenalds... Not to put too fine a point on it, but it\'s got quite a fine point on it. It\'s deadly, is what we\'re saying here."};
descriptions["17490"]={cn:"秘银矿轻盈而坚韧，四大地赐予窝们疯兔的完美材料。\n- 疯兔斯基，著名的皮草商",en:"\"Mythwil owe is incwedibly shiny, wesistant, and pewfect fow evewything we Wabbits make!\"\n-Hollow-Tooth, famed Wabbit furrier"};
descriptions["17491"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["17492"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["17494"]={cn:"海尔伯格伯爵，一名绝无仅有的时间法师！若有敌人胆敢激怒他，他会毫不犹豫地给以反击！",en:"Jacquemart Astron Harebourg, a.k.a. Count Harebourg, is a Xelor like no other! And when his enemies tick, tick, tick him off... he doesn\'t waste any time raising the alarm!"};
descriptions["17495"]={cn:"这个贵族独自一人在他的冰霜之岛上度过了无数个漫长的严冬。\n不过，一旦有入侵者打扰了伯爵的清梦，他绝对不是省油的灯！",en:"This aristocrat\'s mind has been frozen solid by centuries spent all alone on his frozen island.\nBut if anyone intrudes upon the Count\'s solitude, he\'ll be hot on their heels!"};
descriptions["17496"]={cn:"可以开启开关，把敌人弹飞。",en:"This bow can be used to activate switches in the Wabbit Temple and also simply to push an enemy away."};
descriptions["17498"]={cn:"很难获取的徽章。坚持每一天！你的努力一定会得到回报的！",en:"This insignia was mighty hard to obtain, but the power and prestige it brings you make it worth the wait!"};
descriptions["17499"]={cn:"每一位兔奶奶的厨房里必备的一本书。",en:"An antique volume of a undeniable beast-seller that you\'ll find in the kitchen of any Gwandma Wabbit."};
descriptions["17500"]={cn:"可以容纳25只宠物。",en:"This pocket-sized cage has room inside for up to 25 pets."};
descriptions["17515"]={cn:"前往者喱派对！\n打开地图，找到小船！",en:"Head for the Full Jellix Party!\nCheck your map to find the boat!"};
descriptions["17516"]={cn:"既软又硬，就像新鲜的胡萝卜！",en:"A throne that is, at the same time, hard and soft - like a fresh Cawwot!"};
descriptions["17522"]={cn:"你熟知正义，贯彻正义，堪称正义先锋！",en:"You know justice like the back of your hand!"};
descriptions["17525"]={cn:"小毛豆轻轻一抖，酒馆的外形就被改变了。",en:"This Blueprint will enable you to change the appearance of your Inn in two shakes of a Rotcere\'s torso."};
descriptions["17527"]={cn:"这把金色的钥匙能让你进入兔皇帝城堡的王座殿。",en:"This golden-orange key lets you access the Wa\'s Throne Room in the Wa Wabbit\'s Castle dungeon."};
descriptions["17528"]={cn:"古老的雕塑象征着福狸王的信使。已经被新碑取代，但是很有怀旧风。",en:"This ancient statue represents the Lenald Empelol\'s messenger. It\'s long since been replaced by something more recent, but the nostalgic appreciate it."};
descriptions["17529"]={cn:"胡萝卜和黑胡萝卜的结合体。风味独特。",en:"Several types of Cawwots and Black Cawwots were simmered together for hours, which gives an exquisite taste to the dish."};
descriptions["17530"]={cn:"兔皇帝最爱的甜点！只融于口，不融于手。",en:"The Wa\'s favorite treat! Melts in your mouth (and not anywhere else)."};
descriptions["17531"]={cn:"还温着呢。",en:"A blood sample that\'s still warm."};
descriptions["17533"]={cn:"被福狸重新改造过！一头很锋利，另一头更锋利。简直是致命武器。",en:"It\'s been entirely redesigned by the Lenalds! Not to put too fine a point on it, but it\'s got quite a fine point on it. It\'s deadly, is what we\'re saying here."};
descriptions["17534"]={cn:"十支鹅毛笔，十五瓶墨水，再来一堆纸张，好了，你也是文人了。",en:"Ten ruined quills, fifteen bottles of ink and a mountain of scrunched-up paper later, you\'re finally rewarded for your beautiful writing!"};
descriptions["17535"]={cn:"浓缩黑胡萝卜汁兑水而成，别喝太猛，小心小命不保。只有在疯兔岛上的自助榨汁机才能制作。",en:"This drink is extremely loaded with Black Cawwot concentrate. Don\'t breath it in too deeply, or you\'ll lose your head.\nOnly craftable with the Histoholic Marquee on Wabbit Island."};
descriptions["17536"]={cn:"这是一种神秘的物质，经正确调制后，可使你对怪异肿瘤免疫。",en:"This mysterious substance, once properly prepared, will make you immune to the effects of Myxomawosis."};
descriptions["17537"]={cn:"空瓶子，随你装什么，只要它装得下。",en:"An empty vial that you can fill with whatever you want - assuming, of course, it fits in a vial."};
descriptions["17538"]={cn:"抗毒疫苗是以上古孢子为原料调配而成的。几滴就能让你对怪异肿瘤完全免疫。",en:"Antimawosis is a preparation of Spowomawoses. Just a few drops will make you immune to Myxomawosis."};
descriptions["17539"]={cn:"只有那些有着特别的优良传统的人才能获得这个称号！",en:"A title earned by only the best (and shyest) historians of all time!"};
descriptions["17540"]={cn:"袋子上贴着一张字条：这是储备娘，别再往自己嘴你塞呢！",en:"A note is attached to the packet: Should be in the leselve. Stop stuffing youl face."};
descriptions["17543"]={cn:"柔软的披风，可以不穿内衣贴身穿着！一种展现男子汉气概的优雅方式...",en:"This cape has a reputation for legendary softness, which means you can wear it without any underwear! An elegant way to expose yourself..."};
descriptions["17544"]={cn:"曾经属于熊猫武僧首领张·冰雪美酒。因为缺少实验志愿者，他不得已只能自己来试用斗笠，测试它作为尿壶的隐藏功能。",en:"The Solomonk used to belong to an old Pandawa chief who was an expert in laxative potions. Lacking willing subjects, he had to test the potions himself, and used it as a chamber pot."};
descriptions["17545"]={cn:"坠饰里流出美味粘稠的蜂蜜，但现在它看起来更像冰冻蜂蜜。放心，不会流得你全身，只会流到上半身。",en:"Sticky and delicious honey once flowed from this amulet, but now it looks more like iced honey. One thing is sure: it won\'t leak all over your torso."};
descriptions["17546"]={cn:"一场豪赌的产物，赢的那一方取走了这条闪亮的腰带。",en:"This magnificent belt is the result of a mad bet to restore one of the most beautiful belts ever created in Amakna: the Powerful Dazzling Belt! Pakape Promethe won the contest."};
descriptions["17547"]={cn:"用它来创造一件传奇装备。",en:"This seal allows you to create an uncommon belt."};
descriptions["17549"]={cn:"风靡疯兔界的时尚零食。尺寸够大，经常用来当盾牌。",en:"Some Cawwots are for munchin\', some are for defendin\'."};
descriptions["17550"]={cn:"如何用难以想象的力量制造一条独一无二的腰带？看这本书吧。",en:"Here\'s a book which lists the components necessary when crafting an antique belt of unimaginable power."};
descriptions["17551"]={cn:"毛豆制造，制作工艺及配方至今未公开。要清理庇护领地？用毛弹吧。",en:"The formula for this bomb, created by the Rotceres, is secret, but rest assured it\'ll take care of all the monsters around it."};
descriptions["17552"]={cn:"虽然其貌不扬，但是它真的可以让你的臀部十分舒适。",en:"Doesn\'t look like much, but it really makes your butt feel good. Don\'t put any decorations behind the back of the stool."};
