descriptions["17576"]={cn:"宠物染料可以于宠物设定介面中更改。此物品已无用处，可以将其分解掉。",en:"Pet colorings can be changed in the pet settings interface. This item is obsolete; you can recycle it."};
descriptions["17577"]={cn:"传说凤凰会最终熄灭然后在灰烬中重生。但是你的命比它短得多，肯定见不到这一奇迹了。",en:"The legend says the Phoenix burns up and is reborn from the ashes. But it lives for so long that you\'ll never get to see that happen."};
descriptions["17578"]={cn:"一柄奇怪的冰霜镐...",en:"A strange, frozen pickaxe..."};
