descriptions["17593"]={cn:"毛豆制造，制作工艺及配方至今未公开。要清理庇护领地？用毛弹吧。",en:"The formula for this bomb, created by the Rotceres, is secret, but rest assured it\'ll take care of all the monsters around it."};
descriptions["17601"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["17605"]={cn:"做工粗糙的大斧，并不是高端货。",en:"This basic axe isn\'t really the stuff of legends."};
descriptions["17612"]={cn:"洗澡的时候也不用取下来。紧贴皮肤，肥皂沫会在上面惬意地转圈。",en:"No need to take it off when you shower - this amulet sticks to you so well, you won\'t even feel it and the soap will just slide right over it."};
descriptions["17613"]={cn:"敌人来临的时候，使劲抽他！使劲！",en:"When an enemy comes along, you must whip it! Whip it good!"};
descriptions["17614"]={cn:"多亏了强力的胶水，这对肩甲得以呆在你的肩膀上。只是取不下来了。",en:"These epaulettes stay on thanks to some very powerful suckers; they\'re so powerful it\'s very hard to remove the armor."};
descriptions["17615"]={cn:"长满浮游生物，线头都变成了触手。",en:"This cape is the epitome of aquatic symbiosis. The tentacles have fused with the soaked fabric."};
descriptions["17616"]={cn:"为什么瞎子还要带头带？当然是为了拉风。",en:"Why put a bandana over your eyes when you already can\'t see without it? For decoration, obviously!"};
descriptions["17617"]={cn:"用来敲别人脑袋，效果拔群。",en:"Do you find yourself needing a little excitement? Smack Slim\'s Stick into someone\'s head! That oughta fix things."};
descriptions["17618"]={cn:"咕哩，你什么意思？",en:"What\'s the pig idea?"};
descriptions["17619"]={cn:"完全由皮肤制造。虽然闻起来有点怪，但是能保持你的皮肤干爽！",en:"These overalls are made entirely of skin! True, it smells a bit more than latex, but it hydrates your skin so well!"};
descriptions["17620"]={cn:"鱼翅也可以拿来做披风...别吹了，你肯定不知道。",en:"Betcha didn\'t know cod had wings, didja? Shows what you know, don\'t it?"};
descriptions["17621"]={cn:"为海洋生物特别设计，防止海洋生物的皮肤接触空气，",en:"This breastplate was specially designed to protect marine skin from contact with the air."};
descriptions["17622"]={cn:"曾经属于奔波儿霸过往的敌人。奔波儿霸将他们身体的大部分都消化了，剩下没消化的部分都归你。",en:"This medallion is mostly pieced together from the remains of several of Decepticon\'s previous enemies. The rest are things he wasn\'t able to digest."};
descriptions["17623"]={cn:"指环里藏着一小戳海洋生物油，让你随时可以化身变形女。",en:"This ring hides a small supply of marine-oil makeup. To help you get that \"Vicki Nimaj\" look!"};
descriptions["17624"]={cn:"终结者是唯一可以听到哈维斯发出声音的人。也许这是因为终结者在水底下冬眠了太久的缘故...",en:"Merkator is the only one to hear the voices, and communicates with them through his ring. It probably has something to do with his long isolation underwater."};
descriptions["17625"]={cn:"上古时代制造的长靴。防水性能良好。",en:"These boots are a prototype created a long time ago, but they\'re still great for traveling underwater."};
descriptions["17626"]={cn:"穿上它，你也不会变成小萝卜特·泥塘。",en:"This helmet features J.A.R.N.O. Now you can talk to yourself all day like a... well, like Merkator does."};
descriptions["17627"]={cn:"只有那个内裤外穿的家伙才不用腰带。",en:"This amazing belt can scan all the grains of sand in any particular underwater area, but it no longer keeps a total of grains scanned. So... not very useful."};
descriptions["17628"]={cn:"小毛豆轻轻一抖，公会大厅的外形就被改变了。",en:"This Blueprint will enable you to change the appearance of your guild in two shakes of a Rotcere\'s torso."};
descriptions["17629"]={cn:"小毛豆轻轻一抖，公会大厅的外形就被改变了。",en:"This Blueprint will enable you to change the appearance of your guild in two shakes of a Rotcere\'s torso."};
descriptions["17630"]={cn:"小毛豆轻轻一抖，公会大厅的外形就被改变了。",en:"This Blueprint will enable you to change the appearance of your guild in two shakes of a Rotcere\'s torso."};
descriptions["17631"]={cn:"小毛豆轻轻一抖，公会大厅的外形就被改变了。",en:"This Blueprint will enable you to change the appearance of your guild in two shakes of a Rotcere\'s torso."};
descriptions["17657"]={cn:"芬里斯将风度和举止教授给了酷洛宇宙的居民。正是在他的影响下，女人们会连续几个小时独占浴室...",en:"Fhenris teaches the Krosmoz\'s inhabitants about style and bearing. It\'s his influence that makes ladies monopolize the bathroom for hours on end..."};
descriptions["17659"]={cn:"在近身恶战中，你不能用棍子与之抗衡！",en:"When it comes to vicious close-quarters combat, you can\'t beat this one with a stick!"};
descriptions["17660"]={cn:"这把剑不会给予你神力，也不会把我干掉的那些敌人的力量转移到你身上，但是可以用它来砍掉脑袋，这对我们来说足够好了！",en:"This sword won\'t make you immortal; nor will it give you the powers of the enemies you slay using it. But it chops heads pretty well, which is something it itself."};
descriptions["17665"]={cn:"赋予你斗哞士的荣耀！",en:"This costume is a trophy for the best adventurers in Hispañia."};
descriptions["17666"]={cn:"你变得不安分，双脚到处走。",en:"You let your feet wander everywhere they\'re not supposed to."};
descriptions["17667"]={cn:"好好睡个安稳觉吧，虽然总感觉床底下有什么东西。",en:"It\'s almost certain you won\'t sleep tonight since it\'s even more certain there\'s a monster under this bed."};
descriptions["17668"]={cn:"这座墓穴太精美了，结果就被盗墓了。",en:"It used to be a Ghast niche before being stolen due to its decorative qualities."};
descriptions["17669"]={cn:"也就可以放放衣服吧。",en:"The better to sort your clothes with."};
descriptions["17670"]={cn:"这块屏风具备一个发声系统，可以为你营造恐怖的氛围。注意：一旦开启无法关闭。",en:"An audio component has been added to this screen in order to give your interiors an obnoxious feel. It\'s easy to turn on, hard to turn off."};
descriptions["17671"]={cn:"这年头连家具都流行扮鬼了啊！",en:"Even your closets are dying to take part in the Al Howin festivities."};
descriptions["17672"]={cn:"放在空心南瓜里做成南瓜灯。",en:"The candle gives off a slight odor of Pumpkwin."};
descriptions["17673"]={cn:"围坐一圈，开始招魂吧。",en:"To get into that Al Howin spirit, you just need to sit around this table. That\'s all there is to it."};
descriptions["17674"]={cn:"失眠症没治了。",en:"This magic charm could very well be the cause of your insomnia."};
descriptions["17675"]={cn:"不给糖就捣乱！不捣乱就给糖！",en:"Perfect for trick-or-treater catch-and-release."};
descriptions["17676"]={cn:"每看一眼都觉得慎得慌。",en:"You break out in a cold sweat every time you look at this plant!"};
descriptions["17677"]={cn:"现在你的书本都有归属了！",en:"A well-perched bookshelf for all your brightly colored books."};
descriptions["17678"]={cn:"经历过了这么多怪物的试炼，你配得上这件时装。",en:"A well-deserved costume, given the hardships you\'ve been put through by many monsters and particularly by Katrina."};
descriptions["17679"]={cn:"南瓜节怪物猎人，卡特里娜送给你一只绵球骷髅。永远别忘了她。",en:"Katrina Slevastan, Al Howin monster huntress, was nice enough to give you a Gobball Skull. A souvenir so you never forget her."};
descriptions["17680"]={cn:"南瓜节怪物们集会的时候用来点蜡烛的。",en:"This candelabra is frequently used during occult seances organized by Al Howin monsters."};
descriptions["17681"]={cn:"底座上是个骷髅，由食尸鬼的耳蜡制成。",en:"This candle is supported by skulls and is made from Ghoul earwax."};
descriptions["17682"]={cn:"碰上僵尸入侵或者世界末日的时候用。打开来用！不是叫你扔出去。",en:"Quite useful in the event of an all-out, brain-starved Zombie invasion! Or it would be, if you could open it..."};
descriptions["17683"]={cn:"有些木棺用于埋葬死者，有些则被用作床铺，还有的被用作装载各种骷髅...",en:"Some are used to bury the dead, others are used as comfortable beds, and still others are used to store skulls of all shapes and sizes."};
descriptions["17684"]={cn:"被压得扁平的南瓜，以适应各种不同口味。",en:"This Pumpkwin was mercilessly stomped flat, to appeal to certain deviant tastes."};
descriptions["17685"]={cn:"邪恶，是形容这个南瓜的最好词汇。",en:"Diabolic would be the best way to describe this smile. But impish, evil, malevolent, haunting, and possessed would work also."};
descriptions["17686"]={cn:"恐怖，是形容这个南瓜的最好词汇。",en:"Terrifying would be the best way to describe this Pumpkwin\'s gaze. But impish, evil, malevolent, haunting, and possessed would work also."};
descriptions["17687"]={cn:"新鲜出墓，来自无头骸骨。",en:"Freshly exhumed, this skull belongs to the Headless Chafer."};
descriptions["17688"]={cn:"对于卡特里娜来说十分珍贵。她在收集绵球骷髅，准备装饰新家。",en:"This Gobball Skull is rather valuable in Katrina Slevastan\'s eyes. She collects them for interior decorating."};
descriptions["17689"]={cn:"这人睡前总是带着微笑。",en:"This Chafer fell asleep with a smile on his face."};
descriptions["17690"]={cn:"参杂着南瓜的味道和绵球的膻味。",en:"This wool smells of fresh Pumpkwin and not-as-fresh Gobball sweat."};
descriptions["17691"]={cn:"散发出一股混合着南瓜汁和食尸鬼口水的味道。",en:"This emulsion smells like smashed Pumpkwin and putrid Ghoul breath."};
descriptions["17694"]={cn:"你是最佳猎头。",en:"You can claim that you\'ve collected the most heads."};
descriptions["17695"]={cn:"这人的一生一定很快乐。",en:"This Chafer was always happy in life."};
descriptions["17696"]={cn:"一个结实的骷髅，只是死了！",en:"Now that\'s one content Chafer, despite being dead and all!"};
descriptions["17697"]={cn:"现在谁都知道你是坏蛋胚子了。",en:"Now the whole World will know you as the nastiest no-goodnik around."};
descriptions["17698"]={cn:"无畏的骑士，你就是传奇！",en:"You\'re a valiant and legendary knight!"};
descriptions["17699"]={cn:"你就是南瓜节的贵族。",en:"You\'re Al Howin nobility!"};
descriptions["17700"]={cn:"柔软舒适天然记忆乳胶慢回弹，只要998。",en:"The Pandawa mattress is firm yet soft, which helps maintain proper back support while accommodating an ample belly."};
descriptions["17701"]={cn:"箱子里塞满了空酒瓶。",en:"This case is nearly overflowing - with empty bottles."};
descriptions["17702"]={cn:"竹子做的，饿了好啃几口。",en:"A beautiful dresser made of noble Cherry Tree Wood."};
descriptions["17703"]={cn:"熊猫，萌王。",en:"Aren\'t all these little Pandawa heads cute?"};
descriptions["17704"]={cn:"玩躲熊猫游戏的时候用的，可是这啤酒肚，真心躲不进去啊喂！",en:"This big cupboard lets you hide your vital resources in the bottom. Like bottles of beer."};
descriptions["17705"]={cn:"点上一盏灯，陷入平静的沉思之中。",en:"A lamp sure to induce a calm and meditative state."};
descriptions["17706"]={cn:"乱得找不到什么空间放杯子啊。",en:"It\'s entirely possible not to find space on a Pandawa\'s table to set down even a small glass of water."};
descriptions["17707"]={cn:"很明显，里面的酒不是谁都能喝的，偷喝后果自负。",en:"This beer reserve is only to be drunk by its owner; those that drink without permission do so at their own risk."};
descriptions["17708"]={cn:"这游戏怎么玩？告诉你：喂熊猫吃竹子，吃得越多越好。",en:"Who will be the hungriest Pandawa?\nYou have to make your Pandawa swallow the most balls by slapping its backside."};
descriptions["17709"]={cn:"传说中的东方古树...的缩小版，很难养，记得浇水。",en:"This plant, which looks quite a bit like a mini Cherry Tree, is persnickety. You have to constantly sprinkle sand around it, and only give it a couple drops of rain water."};
descriptions["17711"]={cn:"用来展示你最喜欢的时装，时尚万岁！",en:"An incredible fashion dummy to proudly display your loveliest sets, costumes and insignia. You\'re set for life!"};
descriptions["17712"]={cn:"用来展示你最喜欢的时装，时尚万岁！",en:"An incredible fashion dummy to proudly display your loveliest sets, costumes and insignia. You\'re set for life!"};
descriptions["17713"]={cn:"虽然有点破损，但是像第二层皮肤一样，完好地保护着主人。",en:"A bit worn but well woven, this costume is like a second skin."};
descriptions["17714"]={cn:"触手系。",en:"This costume has tentacles... big tentacles..."};
descriptions["17715"]={cn:"有股猪肉味。",en:"This costume smells a bit like pork..."};
descriptions["17716"]={cn:"你比任何时候都更拉风！",en:"You\'re more beautiful than ever in this costume!"};
descriptions["17717"]={cn:"欢迎来到未来！",en:"Welcome to the costume of the future!"};
descriptions["17718"]={cn:"无法抑制的恶意。",en:"You can\'t help feeling evil in this costume."};
descriptions["17719"]={cn:"正义未必胜！",en:"Good doesn\'t always triumph!"};
descriptions["17720"]={cn:"正义必胜！",en:"Good will always triumph!"};
descriptions["17725"]={cn:"超级英雄们在这张桌子上开会。",en:"The perfect table around which to host your meetings of Super Nice Guys!"};
descriptions["17727"]={cn:"贝老伯交给你这把钥匙，去侦察一下那里吧。",en:"Pappy Pal has given you this key for a reconnaissance mission."};
descriptions["17728"]={cn:"械勒居然拨动了圣钟！这家伙疯了吗？",en:"Xelor has reset the divine clock. Who does that dude think he is?!"};
descriptions["17729"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few grains should suffice."};
descriptions["17730"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced, anosmic trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few grains should suffice."};
descriptions["17732"]={cn:"面向贵族阶层的法杖。装备起来，即便是在战斗中，你也觉得自己好像变成了贵族。",en:"This staff was made with the upper classes in mind. Equip it and you\'ll feel like a nobleman, even in the middle of a bloody battle."};
descriptions["17733"]={cn:"修道院里的僧侣们会为了这套卡牌抢破头。",en:"These cards are highly regarded by the monks that collect them in the monastery."};
descriptions["17734"]={cn:"这些小刀片只有在满月的时候才能杀杀狼，其他时候是完全绝对没有用的。",en:"These little blades only slice up Boowolves when there is a full moon. The rest of the time they\'re completely and utterly useless."};
descriptions["17735"]={cn:"锋利的匕首，背刺利器。",en:"This Crobak feather is pretty darn sharp and comes in handy for back-stabbing."};
descriptions["17736"]={cn:"牧师们团结的象征。",en:"This sword looks like it might cause almighty pain but it unites the clergymen all the same."};
descriptions["17737"]={cn:"你将会是下一个幸运之星。",en:"A whack from this sword will hit your enemies like a bolt from the blue."};
descriptions["17738"]={cn:"我一直以为乌鸦是黑的，直到我膝盖中了一箭。",en:"This arc has a large range and launches as the crow flies."};
descriptions["17740"]={cn:"即便是已死之人，也能杀给你看。",en:"They say that this hammer can kill dead people a second time over."};
descriptions["17741"]={cn:"酷洛大师收藏品。",en:"Use this figurine to add it to your Krosmaster collection."};
descriptions["17742"]={cn:"酷洛大师收藏品。",en:"Use this figurine to add it to your Krosmaster collection."};
descriptions["17743"]={cn:"狼祭司用配偶的颅骨制成了这柄法杖。魔力并不强，但我保证你会记住管家婆的力量。",en:"Boowolfines make these staffs from the skulls of their former spouses. They might not be very magical, but they will make sure you never forget who wears the pants."};
descriptions["17744"]={cn:"无论敌人说什么，它都能用“呵呵”两个字来抵挡...真是无懈可击。",en:"Nope, this shield won\'t scream \"GG!!!\" every time you protect yourself with it... Unearthed deep within a Wabbit warren, you can\'t help wondering how it got down there."};
descriptions["17745"]={cn:"华丽地致命一击，让敌人永眠。",en:"Put your enemies to sleep with one fatal blow from this marvelous blade."};
descriptions["17746"]={cn:"选择银河魔杖，变身上流人士！",en:"Join the Elite! Choose a Battlestick Galaktika."};
descriptions["17747"]={cn:"重量和一头死去的哞哞差不多，能防水防狼。有时候，巨魔们甚至将它用作镜子。",en:"The Foolmoun weighs about as much as a dead Moogrr, but it\'s waterproof and resistant to Boowolf scratches. Sometimes, Trools even use it as a mirror."};
descriptions["17748"]={cn:"这个披风能让你的功夫变得更厉害。",en:"This cape will surely augment your martial arts skills."};
descriptions["17749"]={cn:"精英之选，倍加呵护。",en:"This cape will, without a doubt, assure your safety."};
descriptions["17750"]={cn:"畜生禁用。",en:"Not for brutes."};
descriptions["17752"]={cn:"穿着这件胸甲，你可以去冰山岛转一圈。当然并不保证你可以活着回来。",en:"It\'s been said that with this breastplate, you could stroll around Frigost almost completely naked. Note the word \"survive\" was not mentioned."};
descriptions["17753"]={cn:"现在，绵球的荣耀由你来承担了。",en:"Now, the weight of the wool is on your shoulders. Ancient Gobball Hunter proverb"};
descriptions["17754"]={cn:"冬天，也许会有喵喵躲到你头上取暖。",en:"One thing is certain: if you come across a Bow Meow, it will curl up for a nice nap in your warm headgear."};
descriptions["17755"]={cn:"牢牢套在手指上，完全取不下来。",en:"This ring will wear your fingers to the bone."};
descriptions["17756"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["17757"]={cn:"聪明的人永远不会惹这柄法杖的主人。",en:"The wise man admits he knows nothing. He also doesn\'t mess with someone wielding this staff."};
descriptions["17758"]={cn:"拿起这把战锤，你脑子里只剩一个念头：战！",en:"With this hammer you have one and only one desire: smash, smash and SMASH!"};
descriptions["17759"]={cn:"散发着一股恶臭。",en:"This belt is as warm as it is odorous."};
descriptions["17760"]={cn:"你需要一点活力！",en:"If you want to be the very best, you\'re going to need some Vitality!"};
descriptions["17761"]={cn:"必须经过加工才能使用。",en:"This thick skin needs to be refined into leather before you can use it to create equipment."};
descriptions["17762"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["17763"]={cn:"带来幸福。",en:"It brings happiness, or so they say!"};
descriptions["17764"]={cn:"用于驯养野性绵球。坐下！我说坐下！等等，不许放屁，我说的是坐下！",en:"A pretty kennel for a nice, obedient Wild Gobball. Sit! I said sit! No, wait, no, don\'t do that, no, sit!!!!"};
descriptions["17765"]={cn:"小心别再被困在里面了。",en:"Be careful not to get trapped in it forever more."};
descriptions["17766"]={cn:"一种体型相当大的动物的雕像。",en:"A \"miniature\" of a rather voluminous animal."};
descriptions["17767"]={cn:"踢别人屁股的上佳选择。",en:"The wilder the Great Gobball was, the more getting kicked in the butt with these boots will hurt."};
descriptions["17768"]={cn:"野性绵球的一块骨头，魔力有待证明。",en:"Although it\'s a real Wild Gobball bone, its magic virtues remain to be proven."};
descriptions["17769"]={cn:"如各位期待的一样，一股骚味。值得一提的是，它还能用来放一只鸡蛋。",en:"There used to be something inlaid in this necklace. Doesn\'t matter - now it can be used as an eggcup."};
descriptions["17770"]={cn:"即便是野兽也可以很有型！",en:"Even wild animals can have a bit of class!"};
descriptions["17771"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["17772"]={cn:"有点丑陋，但是很神秘的图腾。",en:"It\'s mysterious. Ugly, but mysterious!"};
descriptions["17773"]={cn:"能射出带有臭气的强力弓矢。",en:"Can shoot odoriferous and, frankly, disgusting arrows."};
descriptions["17774"]={cn:"你肯定听过大脚的名字。这靴子穿起来有点潮，最好还是别去研究是由什么材料做成的。",en:"You\'ve never heard of this Feesy, but these boots keep your feet nice and toasty... They\'re a bit wet too, but it\'s probably best not to think about that too much."};
descriptions["17775"]={cn:"别放下，说不定就跑了！",en:"Don\'t let go; it might take off running!"};
descriptions["17776"]={cn:"腐烂胡萝卜制成的匕首，在僵尸兔的地盘找到的...应该很厉害。",en:"A dagger made of a rotten Cawwot that was found in Zwombbit territory... It\'ll do the trick."};
descriptions["17777"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["17778"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["17779"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["17782"]={cn:"你选了这块护盾！你真聪明！",en:"Your wisdom can be seen in your choice of arms."};
descriptions["17783"]={cn:"从伤痛中学到经验还是干脆防止受伤，这取决于你。",en:"Turn your wounds into wisdom. Or carry a shield and avoid wounds. Your choice."};
descriptions["17784"]={cn:"破损不堪，无法辨识。说不清是一块抹布还是一块手绢，也许更糟...",en:"This stained scrap of fabric isn\'t really identifiable. You can\'t tell from the stains if it\'s a used tissue, a pair of skidmarked boxers, or worse still. But what could be worse?"};
descriptions["17785"]={cn:"别误会，并不是野性绵球的犄角。这是Jc年轻时候想刷的一件物品，很难掉，不过也没什么大不了的，对吧。记住，不是野性绵球的犄角。",en:"This horn wasn\'t torn from Kiki, the Bwoggall \"appropriated\" by Thork. It\'s a hunting trophy from Thork\'s youth, a good luck charm of sorts. However, the fact that you have it would seem to indicate that its influence isn\'t linked to luck. At least, not the good kind."};
descriptions["17786"]={cn:"用于制造装备。",en:"This Spit Toon can be used in the fabrication of equipment."};
descriptions["17787"]={cn:"当你与狼共舞的时候，这双靴子可以让你轻松一点儿。",en:"These boots will make it that little bit easier to dance with Boowolves."};
descriptions["17788"]={cn:"一个人走夜路时记得带着这枚护符。",en:"This lucky amulet will protect you from those uneasy midnight encounters."};
descriptions["17789"]={cn:"在森林里穿会显得很可怕，能展现你隐藏的狂野一面。",en:"This mask can be pretty terrifying\nif worn in the forestand will really bring out your wild side."};
descriptions["17790"]={cn:"切忌食用，使用后请洗手。",en:"Keep this out of your mouth and wash your hands after use."};
descriptions["17791"]={cn:"由蓝蓟纤维制成。刺很多，小心手指...",en:"A ring made from woven Thistle fibers. Be careful with your fingers: it\'s probably full of thorns..."};
descriptions["17792"]={cn:"出乎意料，这根指针并没有死去。它习惯杀戮。",en:"Despite what you might think, this clock hand isn\'t actually dead. It just likes killing others."};
descriptions["17793"]={cn:"时间法师使用指针来鼓舞队友，给敌人致命一击。",en:"Acu the Xelor knew how to use his clock hands to awaken his friends\' senses as well as make his enemies suffer excruciating pain."};
descriptions["17794"]={cn:"时间在你掌握之中！想睡多久睡多久！",en:"Now you have The Watch, time is in your hands! You can be as late as you like!"};
descriptions["17795"]={cn:"在上面蹲一会儿，能孵化出一只巧克力豆芙来。",en:"Apparently if you sit on the egg from this necklace, a chocolate Tofu will be born."};
descriptions["17796"]={cn:"不仅能用来招揽盟友，战斗中也很有用。",en:"Whip out this tough, sturdy bone to impress your allies. It\'s pretty useful in combat too."};
descriptions["17797"]={cn:"使你可以挖掘最坚固的岩石。",en:"Allows you to dig through even the toughest rock."};
descriptions["17798"]={cn:"兽人炸弹的一部分。",en:"Part of a Bwork bomb."};
descriptions["17799"]={cn:"兽人炸弹的完成形态。",en:"Complete Bwork Bomb."};
descriptions["17800"]={cn:"穿上它，变身披着狼皮的羊。",en:"You\'ll be like a sheep in Boowolf\'s clothing with this cloak made from real Boowolf skin."};
descriptions["17802"]={cn:"变身成海尔伯格伯爵。",en:"Transforms you into Count Harebourg."};
descriptions["17804"]={cn:"尽管做工粗糙，但是很结实。如果不是臭气熏天的话，战斗中十分好用。",en:"Despite the primitive craftsmanship, this breastplate seems pretty solid. It would be perfect for combat, were it not for the odor of Bwork wafting from literally every surface."};
descriptions["17805"]={cn:"你想得到穿兽人的靴子走一英里的感觉，但是你想不到会留下多少汗水和疼痛...",en:"You\'ve always wanted to walk a mile in a Bwork\'s shoes, but you didn\'t think of the half-inch of scum and sweat that would be left behind... Squelch! but you didn\'t think of the half-inch of scum and sweat that would be left behind... Squelch! Urgh!"};
descriptions["17806"]={cn:"据说兽人从来不脱衣服和头盔，也不会洗衣服和头盔，更不会洗澡...",en:"Some say the Bworks never take their armor off and never wash it. They never wash themselves either, for that matter."};
descriptions["17807"]={cn:"兽人都爱棕色。他们用野性绵球绒毛制成了这件披风。好吧，这只是个谣言。你绝对不想知道这件披风是用什么做的。",en:"It\'s said that the leather used in making this cape was tanned using the secretions of a Wild Gobball. This is only a rumor though. The truth is far worse."};
descriptions["17808"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["17809"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["17810"]={cn:"索克爱喝啤酒。索克也很笨拙。他的胸甲上一股子酒味。",en:"Thork likes Bwork beer. But Thork is very clumsy. Which can be seen, and smelt, on his breastplate."};
descriptions["17811"]={cn:"简洁有用，结实耐操。索克的最爱。",en:"Solid, simple, effective. Thork likes massive epaulettes. That way, he looks like he\'s more than just a Bwork."};
descriptions["17812"]={cn:"由兽人的胡须制成。不起眼，但是很有用。",en:"Thork\'s only apparently useless accessory, the amulet is made of the beard of an ancient Bwork named Nad\'Lug. In actuality, it\'s really powerful."};
descriptions["17813"]={cn:"索克的腰带能防止他的裤子掉落。其实这种情况根本不会发生，因为他“借”来了兽兽球坐骑奇奇。",en:"Thork\'s belt keeps his pants from falling down. Which almost never happens now that he\'s \"borrowed\" Kiki, the Bwoggall mount of the Explorer leader."};
descriptions["17814"]={cn:"靴子上的尖刺给兽人探险者留下了深刻印象。很明显这双靴子踢过很多屁股...",en:"The spikes on Thork\'s boots had always impressed his fellow Bwork Explorers. It\'s plain to see they\'ve been used to kick a few butts..."};
descriptions["17815"]={cn:"兽人的骄傲，兽人力量的象征。这把锤子蕴含了比奥古之乱更加久远的上古时代的神力。锤子的携带者周围会不断地迸发出火花，四溅开来，所以安全起见，一定要按照正确的方式来使用。更多的故事就要去问索克本人了。",en:"A symbol of power and Bwork pride, this hammer is infused with an ancestral power more ancient than Ogrest\'s Chaos. Called the Boomhammer, this weapon is capable of shooting sparks around its user, and sometimes ON the user, if it\'s handled improperly. Thork could tell you all about that last part."};
descriptions["17816"]={cn:"别被名字吓到了。所谓的缠绕物只是一条腰带...据说当年由史上最大的绿皮佩戴。当那个绿皮正常的时候，腰带看起来也很正常。然而，当绿皮狂性大发的时候，这条腰带能在身体膨胀N倍的情况下保持裤子依然贴身不掉落。",en:"Don\'t be fooled by the highfalutin name. It\'s said this \"cincture\" is actually the repurposed toe ring of what must be the biggest Bwork in history. As we all know, as the dimensions of a Bwork increase by a factor of n, Bwork surface area increases by n squared. Much more skin to catch the sun. At the same time, Bwork volumetric mass increases by n cubed. Much, much more fat to soak up the sun and insulate. Which all amounts to a really fat, really sweaty Bwork with a really sweaty toe ring. Lots."};
descriptions["17817"]={cn:"虽然用兽人传统原料制成，但是做工精细，外观整洁...似乎对于兽人的大脑袋来说，不太好套进去啊...",en:"This Bwork amulet is fairly disturbing. Other than the delicateness which it was created with compared to normal Bwork products, it\'s its cleanliness which is most shocking! Oh! But of course. The cord is much too short to go around the head and ears of a Bwork."};
descriptions["17818"]={cn:"简易好用的剑。用来敲打比砍削更实在。只是手柄上很粘，不知道是什么东西...",en:"Simple and effective, this blade is designed more to crush than cut. The only thing that makes you doubt its combat-worthiness is the sticky handle..."};
descriptions["17819"]={cn:"你永远不知道这帮兽人是怎么制造盾牌的...常人难以理解。",en:"You\'ve turned it this way and that, and still cannot understand how they got the iron around the wooden center. Unless they somehow inserted the wooden center into the iron? You may never know..."};
descriptions["17820"]={cn:"法杖的一部分，也许可以插进底座。",en:"This staff could be part of the key to using the model."};
descriptions["17821"]={cn:"法杖的一部分，完成后可以插入底座。",en:"This headpiece could be part of the key to using the model"};
descriptions["17822"]={cn:"能完美嵌入底座。",en:"It seems to fit perfectly in the Bwork model."};
descriptions["17828"]={cn:"臭...",en:"That charming, refined scent of Bwork."};
descriptions["17829"]={cn:"绵道夫也救不了你了。",en:"Choice pieces that Bwork Cook would be more than happy to cook."};
descriptions["17830"]={cn:"可口的啤酒，只是有股氨水味。",en:"A beer with a delicious hint of ammonia."};
descriptions["17831"]={cn:"传统的兽人风味汉堡。",en:"All the flavors of traditional Bwork cuisine, condensed into a burger."};
descriptions["17832"]={cn:"闻起来...你居然真的闻了！",en:"It doesn\'t smell great... In fact, it smells horrid."};
descriptions["17833"]={cn:"不太结实。最好别在凳子后面放任何东西。",en:"Despite what you may think, the pieces of this stool have not been properly screwed together. Don\'t put any decorations behind the back of the stool."};
descriptions["17834"]={cn:"胡萝卜做的凳子腿，也许不太安稳。千万别在上面放任何会引来疯兔的饰物！",en:"The table legs, being made out of Cawwot, can be a bit unstable.\nDon\'t put any decorations behind the back of the stool."};
descriptions["17835"]={cn:"宝藏老头子歇脚的神器，臭脚丫子亮出来！",en:"Great for Enutrofs who like to give their legs a rest or just admire their socks-and-sandals combo. Don\'t put any decorations behind the back of the seat."};
descriptions["17836"]={cn:"宝藏老头子歇脚的神器，臭脚丫子亮出来！",en:"Great for Enutrofs who like to give their legs a rest or just admire their socks-and-sandals combo. Don\'t put any decorations behind the back of the seat."};
