descriptions["17847"]={cn:"穿上它，你可以放心追寻上古遗迹...",en:"A costume to let you pursue archaosology safely..."};
descriptions["17848"]={cn:"穿上它，你可以放心追寻上古遗迹...",en:"A costume to let you pursue archaosology safely..."};
descriptions["17849"]={cn:"穿上它，你可以放心追寻上古遗迹...",en:"A costume to let you pursue archaosology safely..."};
descriptions["17850"]={cn:"穿上它，你可以放心追寻上古遗迹...",en:"A costume to let you pursue archaosology safely..."};
descriptions["17851"]={cn:"杖头碎片。\n收集3块杖头碎片，重组叹息法杖的头部。\n任务物品。",en:"Part of a headpiece. \nFuse the 3 parts of the headpiece to reform the Headpiece of Arrrghhh.\nQuest item."};
descriptions["17852"]={cn:"兽兽球比赛用服。",en:"A costume for playing Bworkball."};
descriptions["17856"]={cn:"使你得以摧毁怨灵图腾。",en:"Allows you to destroy Excarnal Totems."};
descriptions["17857"]={cn:"闪耀的红宝石，刚好能嵌入兽人图腾。",en:"A scintillating red gem which would fit perfectly into a Bwork Totem."};
descriptions["17858"]={cn:"闪耀的黄宝石，刚好能嵌入兽人图腾。",en:"A scintillating yellow gem which would fit perfectly into a Bwork Totem."};
descriptions["17859"]={cn:"闪耀的蓝宝石，刚好能嵌入兽人图腾。",en:"A scintillating blue gem which would fit perfectly into a Bwork Totem."};
descriptions["17860"]={cn:"闪耀的绿宝石，刚好能嵌入兽人图腾。",en:"A scintillating green gem which would fit perfectly into a Bwork Totem."};
descriptions["17861"]={cn:"据占星学家，本丹骑士的研究，天上的星星是由面包屑和果酱做成的。",en:"\"Did you know? The stars are actually a subtle mixture of fairy dust and custard!\"\n- Mye Iopik, astrologer"};
descriptions["17862"]={cn:"冒险者必备，保暖佳品，即使常年使用也不会磨损。",en:"This wool is so dense that it can be used over several days. It\'s a must-have for avid explorers."};
descriptions["17863"]={cn:"谁说老面包不好吃的？",en:"Whoever said old bread was bad bread? This stuff is probably totally edible."};
descriptions["17864"]={cn:"使你可以进入兽人挖掘场。小心里面的兽人患者！",en:"Opens the principal Bwork excavation site. Beware the Bwork Foos inside!"};
descriptions["17867"]={cn:"无论你是新手还是老手，作用都很明显。",en:"A potion that\'s bound to come in useful, whether you\'re a fresh-faced beginner or a not-so-fresh-faced pro."};
descriptions["17868"]={cn:"专为兽人探险家的领导者准备的王座，独具匠心。",en:"An artisanal Bwork throne for a great leader of Bwork Explorers."};
descriptions["17869"]={cn:"众所周知，没有什么能比兽人栅栏更让来客觉得宾至如归的了。",en:"It\'s known the world over that there\'s nothing like a good Bwork barrier to make your visitors feel welcome."};
descriptions["17870"]={cn:"回归本来的样子，轻松自在。",en:"Transparent as spring water. It allows you to wear your class\'s default outfit, no matter what gear you\'ve equipped."};
descriptions["17872"]={cn:"授予泪战中的战警英雄！",en:"You bagged this title by winning the Civil Waw contest in the Vigilante category!"};
descriptions["17873"]={cn:"授予泪战中的恶棍英雄！",en:"You bagged this title by winning the Civil Waw contest in the Supervillain category!"};
descriptions["17877"]={cn:"你可以参加任何兽兽球联赛...如果有的话。",en:"With this you could compete in any Bworkball league... assuming one existed."};
descriptions["17878"]={cn:"你可以将 M 战警绑定至你的帐号并在战斗中使用。注意！除去个别特殊情况，这项操作无法被取消。",en:"This item enables you to link this Multiman to your account and use him in combat. Careful! This action cannot be undone, except under certain circumstances."};
