descriptions["18257"]={cn:"魔族火药一箱包邮。",en:"This crate contains some Shushu Smokenmirs more grisly than your Uncle Quasi\'s face."};
descriptions["18258"]={cn:"使用物品栏上方的分解按钮将这件物品回收为附魔碎片。",en:"This item must be converted into shards using the Recycle button at the top of the inventory window."};
descriptions["18259"]={cn:"往里头找找，可能有金子哦...想多了，只摸到一手的灰尘。",en:"If you search the depths of the drawer, maybe you\'ll find gold! Or dust. Probably dust."};
descriptions["18260"]={cn:"可以缓解老年人与卡玛之间过于纠结的关系。",en:"This bed helps healing and the readaptation of the elderly and those who are too attached to their kamas."};
descriptions["18261"]={cn:"收藏大于实用。",en:"This wardrobe is more antique than practical."};
descriptions["18262"]={cn:"很廉价的感觉，用来遮掩背后的财富。",en:"Protects both those with sensitive skin and cheapskates from bodily harm."};
descriptions["18263"]={cn:"好贪婪的桌子！",en:"You\'ll never find as much greed as at this table!"};
descriptions["18264"]={cn:"一款模拟经营类的游戏。",en:"An unusual number of Enutrof games involve counting riches."};
descriptions["18265"]={cn:"一股铜臭味。",en:"This plant masks any old musty odors there might be."};
descriptions["18266"]={cn:"蜡烛很便宜，不点更便宜。",en:"Because candles are cheap, especially when they\'re not lit."};
descriptions["18267"]={cn:"代代相传，破旧不堪。",en:"After having been handed down generation after generation, this stool\'s feet are rather worn out."};
descriptions["18268"]={cn:"愿吉祥的铲子带给它的主人永远的好运。",en:"These good-luck shovels guarantee fortune and long life for their Enutrof owner."};
descriptions["18269"]={cn:"玫瑰香扑来，浪漫满屋！",en:"There are even rose-scented sheets to help move things along."};
descriptions["18270"]={cn:"准备一道浪漫的烛光晚餐。",en:"A candlelit dinner will be sure to charm the one you love."};
descriptions["18271"]={cn:"圣心巧克力大教堂同款凳子，真爱之选。",en:"Ballotwine\'s without a bit of romance wouldn\'t be a celebration of lovers."};
descriptions["18272"]={cn:"真的爱你！",en:"One of the most beautiful ways to declare your love!"};
descriptions["18273"]={cn:"毁灭一切的力量！要是他老人家发现自己的公仔居然被做得这么可爱，一定二话不说毁灭之！",en:"Rushu is imposing and terrifying - if he someday discovers that the stuffed toy version is extremely cute, he\'ll destroy it immediately."};
descriptions["18274"]={cn:"夜长梦多。",en:"Your night will be one long nightmare."};
descriptions["18275"]={cn:"善人免进！",en:"For questionable intimacy."};
descriptions["18276"]={cn:"长了个贼溜溜的眼睛。",en:"It will keep an eye on your most evil plans."};
descriptions["18277"]={cn:"宠物装备可以于宠物设定介面中更改。此物品已无用处，可以将其分解掉。",en:"Pet equipment can be changed in the pet settings interface. This item is obsolete; you can recycle it."};
descriptions["18278"]={cn:"宠物装备可以于宠物设定介面中更改。此物品已无用处，可以将其分解掉。",en:"Pet equipment can be changed in the pet settings interface. This item is obsolete; you can recycle it."};
descriptions["18279"]={cn:"哎呦喂！你穿上这件华丽的黑疯兔时装肯定漂亮极了。我们差点认为你是黑疯兔的一员。",en:"And away we go! This ravishing Black Wabbit costume will look stunning on you. We\'d almost think you were really one of them."};
descriptions["18280"]={cn:"好可爱哦，粉嘟嘟的。",en:"A lovely Gobball costume, in a shade that really brings out your conjunctivitis."};
descriptions["18281"]={cn:"阿紫！阿兹！紫色的阿兹！",en:"A lovely Tofu costume, in a nice, deep purple."};
descriptions["18282"]={cn:"强大的卷轴，将你的技能天赋归零，好让你重新分配。",en:"An extra-special scroll that lets you relearn your elemental spells."};
descriptions["18283"]={cn:"强大的卷轴，将你的角色属性归零，好让你重新分配。",en:"A powerful scroll allowing you to reset your characteristics to zero in order to redistrubute points."};
descriptions["18284"]={cn:"可以用来切火腿...肠。",en:"This sword can cut ham, Enutrofs, amputees, and even Enutrof amputees coated in ham."};
descriptions["18285"]={cn:"别太依赖护盾哦，自己的屁股要自己保护。",en:"This shield won\'t protect you from your own stupidity."};
descriptions["18286"]={cn:"第一次穿上披风的感觉...我相信我能飞！",en:"You\'ll be able to fly with this cape around your shoulders. Just close your eyes, clench your fists, open your mouth, stretch out your arms and jump off a cliff shouting \"I can fly!\"."};
descriptions["18287"]={cn:"罩得住秃顶的头，罩不住犯傻的心。",en:"This shoddy hat admirably hides your baldness. Unfortunately, it\'s not big enough to hide your false modesty."};
descriptions["18288"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["18289"]={cn:"就是它了！百分百魔族主题的庇护袋！",en:"A really shuper kit! It\'ll help discourage those who would venture into your peaceful little haven."};
descriptions["18290"]={cn:"男才女貌，天生一对。",en:"Propose and get shot down in only the most handsome garments!"};
descriptions["18291"]={cn:"有什么？",en:"What item will you get in this mystery box?"};
descriptions["18292"]={cn:"终于发明出来了！一瓶魔药，能让你随意改变模样，甚至性别！",en:"This lets you change your character\'s sex, color and clothes."};
