descriptions["18298"]={cn:"魔族火药一箱包邮。",en:"This crate contains some Shushu Smokenmirs more grisly than your Uncle Quasi\'s face."};
descriptions["18299"]={cn:"恶魔来着。",en:"Evil incarnate."};
descriptions["18300"]={cn:"提取自磨魂者，给你非凡的感觉。",en:"Extracted from the Tormentor, this potion gives rock solid style."};
descriptions["18301"]={cn:"黑暗孢子仓惶逃跑时落下了一把钥匙。真走运！",en:"The Frightened Blackspore seems to have dropped a key in his hurry. What luck!"};
descriptions["18302"]={cn:"烧掉它！看它在灰烬中绽放。",en:"You just have to burn it and give it all your hatred for it to blossom into beauty."};
descriptions["18304"]={cn:"避免仙人刺扎手的痛苦，助你轻松采集仙人浆。",en:"These gloves will protect you from the Juicy Cacti\'s spines while you\'re collecting Juicy Sap."};
descriptions["18305"]={cn:"你记的笔记，帮助你理解掌仙人的语言。",en:"The notes you took to help you understand the Castuc language."};
descriptions["18306"]={cn:"佩戴过久，容易起球，起球过度，变成烟雾。",en:"If worn for too long, this little item can cause funny little puffs that may eventually lead to the systematic disintegration of it wearer into a cloud of Stasis."};
descriptions["18310"]={cn:"4,000枚硬币，因爱铸就。",en:"4,000 little kamas, minted with love."};
descriptions["18313"]={cn:"5,000枚硬币，因爱铸就。",en:"5,000 little kamas, minted with love."};
descriptions["18314"]={cn:"你可以将 M 战警绑定至你的帐号并在战斗中使用。注意！除去个别特殊情况，这项操作无法被取消。",en:"This item enables you to link this sidekick to your account and use it in combat. Careful! This action cannot be undone, except under certain circumstances."};
descriptions["18316"]={cn:"用来展示你最喜欢的服装，时尚万岁！",en:"An incredible fashion dummy to proudly display your loveliest sets, costumes and insignia. You\'re set for life!"};
descriptions["18317"]={cn:"用来展示你最喜欢的服装，时尚万岁！",en:"An incredible fashion dummy to proudly display your loveliest sets, costumes and insignia. You\'re set for life!"};
descriptions["18318"]={cn:"就是它了！百分百斯拉姆主题的庇护袋！骨头棒子挑起来的铺盖卷，刺客带着它去冒险太适合了！",en:"A bindle on the end of a bone is more than enough for a Sram heading out on an adventure!"};
descriptions["18319"]={cn:"百分百纯沙填充，长长的舌头可以随意伸缩！",en:"Its long tongue can be folded up and put back in the mouth. It\'s also filled mostly with 100% genuine sand."};
descriptions["18320"]={cn:"就是它了！百分百凯拉主题的庇护袋！最适合弓箭手！它带有肩带，森林旅行的最佳选择！",en:"This bag is perfect for a Cra! It has pockets just for your arrows, and it\'s great for long treks through the forests!"};
descriptions["18321"]={cn:"就是它了！百分百伊欧普主题的庇护袋！为骑士量身打造，带有有图无字版使用手册，小菜一碟！",en:"As this product is intended for Iops, the creators have wisely chosen to put together an instruction manual containing only pictures and no words. Piece of cake!"};
descriptions["18322"]={cn:"就是它了！百分百欧萨莫达主题的庇护袋！它像刚洗过的宠物毛皮一样柔软！",en:"This bag is as soft as a freshly washed pet\'s fur!"};
descriptions["18323"]={cn:"就是它了！百分百械勒主题的庇护袋！里面装满了齿轮和弹簧！",en:"This bag is chock-full of cogs and springs!"};
descriptions["18324"]={cn:"漂亮的战袍，为初心者定做。",en:"This beautiful costume will make you look classy... for once."};
descriptions["18325"]={cn:"火热的战袍，为好战者准备。",en:"This magnificent costume will make you look classy... for once."};
