descriptions["18327"]={cn:"炫目的战袍，大师专享。",en:"This marvelous costume will make you look classy... for once."};
descriptions["18329"]={cn:"这张床可以保证你不会进入深度睡眠，稍有风吹草动就立刻跳起来迎敌。",en:"This bed will keep you in a shallow sleep, ready to leap out of bed at the slightest sound."};
descriptions["18330"]={cn:"这个行军橱不但能装下你所有的弓箭，还能装一大堆乱七八糟的衣服。",en:"This wardrobe is more than big enough to hold all your extra bows and your wardrobe of nondescript clothes."};
descriptions["18331"]={cn:"它有很多秘密夹层，专门为收藏价值不菲的稀有箭而设计。",en:"This dresser has secret compartments specially designed to hide your rarest and most valuable arrows."};
descriptions["18332"]={cn:"每个弓箭手日常沐浴的时候都会...",en:"Every Cra needs a bit of intimacy during their daily cleansing rituals."};
descriptions["18333"]={cn:"你可以在这张桌子上大口吃沙拉大杯喝水。",en:"A great table at which to eat your green salad with a big glass of water."};
descriptions["18334"]={cn:"呼吸...伸展...格挡...正中靶心！",en:"Breathe... Stretch... Block... Aim center mass!!!"};
descriptions["18335"]={cn:"超赞的凯拉弓箭展架，每一把都是极品。",en:"A fantastic collection of Cra bows. Each and every one a treasure."};
descriptions["18336"]={cn:"拉弓射箭一整天后，让你的疲劳的脚舒缓一下。",en:"A comfortable stool to let you rest your tired legs after a long day of being on your feet, shooting things."};
descriptions["18337"]={cn:"附带香薰，可缓解一天的疲劳。",en:"The Cra lamp creates a mellow atmosphere and relieves tension after a long day."};
descriptions["18338"]={cn:"献给想展现自己萨迪达人一面的凯拉人。",en:"For the Cra who wants to get in touch with his Sadida side."};
descriptions["18339"]={cn:"由麦秸和豆芙羽毛制成，用来蹭掉鞋底的泥土。",en:"This carpet is made of wheat straw and Tofu feathers, which makes it pretty effective at scraping the crud off your boots."};
descriptions["18340"]={cn:"一只又大又漂亮的菜刀正在等着你。",en:"This big and beautiful Fleaster egg is just waiting for you to decorate it."};
descriptions["18341"]={cn:"彩蛋大丰收。",en:"Your egg harvest was pretty good this Fleaster."};
descriptions["18342"]={cn:"散发出牛奶巧克力芳香的漂亮烛台。",en:"A pretty lamp with a gentle milk chocolate aroma that will remind you of Fleasters past."};
descriptions["18343"]={cn:"专门跟彩蛋专用桌配套使用。整天弓腰站着怎么能做出漂亮的彩蛋呢？",en:"This stool is designed specifically to go with the Fleaster Customization Table. It\'s hard to make pretty eggs when you\'re standing hunched over a table, after all."};
