descriptions["18363"]={cn:"你就像黑暗中的烛火，静静地蹲在路边。",en:"In the darkness, you\'re the most terrifying Borbat!"};
descriptions["18365"]={cn:"再也不用到野外去偷窥绵球的私生活了，把这小东西领回去吧。",en:"With this pet, you\'ll be able to count Gobblies any time you\'re having trouble sleeping. You probably won\'t get very far with just one though."};
