descriptions["18376"]={cn:"让宠物与坐骑的等级提高 2 级。",en:"This kibble gives 2 additional levels to pets and mounts."};
descriptions["18377"]={cn:"让你的宠物完全恢复生命。",en:"This kibble refills your pet\'s and petsmount\'s health."};
descriptions["18378"]={cn:"这个饲料能给宠物和坐骑一顿饱饭。",en:"This kibble gives 1 meal to pets and mounts."};
descriptions["18379"]={cn:"这份文件证明你在抵抗失眠的斗争中所立下的丰功伟绩。",en:"This document will let you prove your status as the victor of the Tales of Insomnia."};
descriptions["18380"]={cn:"哈利是个很有智慧的老人，喜欢光着脚钓鱼。终于有一天，在某个漫长的夏日的傍晚，他把自己的靴子忘记在萨弗基亚的码头上了。",en:"Harry was an old wise man who loved to fish with bare feet. Inevitably, after a long summer day, he forgot his boots on the Sufokian docks."};
descriptions["18381"]={cn:"这副肩甲久经沙场。虽然不如从前那么坚固，但是如果你不想武器报废的话，最好不要用力砍它。",en:"These epaulettes have seen more than one battle. They may not look too sturdy, but best not to hit them too hard if you want to keep your weapon."};
descriptions["18382"]={cn:"收集100块碎片，合成哈利波鞋。",en:"Collect 100 of these fragments to create a pair of Harry Boots."};
descriptions["18383"]={cn:"收集100块碎片，合成黑暗弗拉德肩甲。",en:"Collect 100 of these fragments to create a pair of Dark Vlad\'s Epaulettes."};
descriptions["18384"]={cn:"这是那个能让你摧毁兽人神庙怨灵图腾的权杖的升级版。如果你知道正确姿势的话，它应该还有很多其它用途。",en:"This scepter is a better version of the one that lets you make excarnal totems temporarily disappear from the Bwork temple in the Wild Estate. It seems like it would be capable of other things too, provided you know how to handle it."};
descriptions["18385"]={cn:"这是你用来开启兔皇帝城堡开关的那把弓的升级版。如果你知道正确姿势的话，它应该还有很多其它用途。尽管这把弓受到了疯兔的不良影响，仍有很多人认为它是被凯拉女神祝福过的圣物。",en:"This bow is an improved version of the one that lets you activate statues in the Wa\'s Showtcut Temple on Wabbit Island. It seems like it would be capable of other things too, provided you know how to handle it. Despite its obviously Wabbit influences, some people think it\'s actually an artifact blessed by the goddess Cra herself."};
descriptions["18386"]={cn:"布面的光泽让你分不清它是天然如此，还是经过人为加工的。",en:"The shimmering fabric of this poncho actually seems to be pretty resistant, no matter how primitively it appears to have been made."};
descriptions["18387"]={cn:"摸上去轻灵冷冽，助你潜入敌人的背后，突然发起致命一击。",en:"Light and cold to the touch, this spectral dagger seems to invite you to slip behind your enemies and help them to disappear."};
descriptions["18388"]={cn:"这面盾牌中含有海水的成分，让你在战斗中感觉清凉爽快，特别是女朋友没在边上观战的时候。",en:"This magnificent shield contains a few drops of seawater. Not only does it bring good luck but it can also be used as a flask."};
descriptions["18389"]={cn:"你现在可以跟绵球宠物玩耍了。",en:"Now you can play Leap-Gobball with your pet."};
descriptions["18390"]={cn:"只有少数冒险者才配得上这个称号。",en:"This title is only given to adventurers who have truly earned it."};
