descriptions["18395"]={cn:"你就像黑暗中的烛火，静静地蹲在路边。",en:"In the darkness, you\'re the most terrifying Borbat!"};
descriptions["18396"]={cn:"如果不是被你带着扬帆渡海，此刻它应该沉睡在撒哈哈的掌仙人公墓里。",en:"This Castupod ended up in the Ohwymi Desert cemetery and was brought all the way by boat so you could use it as decoration."};
descriptions["18397"]={cn:"如果不是被你带着扬帆渡海，此刻它应该沉睡在撒哈哈的掌仙人公墓里。",en:"This Saguaro ended up in the Ohwymi Desert cemetery and was brought all the way by boat so you could use it as decoration."};
descriptions["18398"]={cn:"嫌毒菇和磷菇太小？这个特大号蘑菇准适合你！",en:"If you think Inkaps and Mushrays are too small, here\'s the XL mushroom that\'s perfect for you!"};
descriptions["18399"]={cn:"隔一段路放一个，很醒目的里程碑。",en:"This blockade is so good at demarcating passages and paths you\'ll be euphoric every time you use it."};
descriptions["18400"]={cn:"收集100块碎片，合成海蓝圆盾。",en:"Collect 100 of these fragments to create an Asse Shield."};
descriptions["18401"]={cn:"这种药水可以提高你150点悟性，持续几场战斗。",en:"This potion increases your Wisdom (XP gain) by 150 for several fights. It can be consumed multiple times to increase the number of fights."};
descriptions["18406"]={cn:"这种药水可以提高你150点勘探，持续几场战斗。",en:"This potion increases your Prospecting by 150 for several fights. It can be consumed multiple times to increase the number of fights."};
descriptions["18422"]={cn:"它能让你活力四射。在战场上没有效果。",en:"This cocktail gives you back all your Vitality. It does not work on Battlefields."};
descriptions["18426"]={cn:"好萌的小东西呀！绝对比现实版萌多了，现实版太恐怖了！",en:"How cute this little toy is! Definitely cuter than the full-sized version, which is, frankly, terrifying."};
descriptions["18427"]={cn:"漂亮的战袍，为初心者定做。",en:"This beautiful costume will make you look classy... for once."};
descriptions["18428"]={cn:"火热的战袍，为好战者准备。",en:"This magnificent costume will make you look classy... for once."};
descriptions["18429"]={cn:"黯淡的战袍，谋略家最爱。",en:"This splendid costume will make you look classy... for once."};
descriptions["18430"]={cn:"炫目的战袍，大师专享。",en:"This marvelous costume will make you look classy... for once."};
descriptions["18431"]={cn:"让你的宠物及坐骑一下升到满级。",en:"A fantastic kibble which will max out your pets\' and mounts\' levels."};
descriptions["18432"]={cn:"独特的徽章，戴起来之后化身萨满。",en:"This emblem carries an exclusive outfit that would look the business on your Masqueraider."};
descriptions["18433"]={cn:"这份文件授予你\"迅捷歼灭者\"称号。",en:"This document will enable you to prove your status as a Swift Exterminator."};
descriptions["18442"]={cn:"和刀片一样锋利，能让你在千钧一发之时脱身。",en:"Here\'s a piece of bone that\'s as sharp as a razor blade and is very useful for getting you out of a close shave with an enemy."};
descriptions["18443"]={cn:"这块碎片带来的兴奋感折磨着你的心灵。",en:"All that excitement in a single fragment really takes its toll on your mental health."};
descriptions["18444"]={cn:"暴力的一击把残留都打得四分五裂。",en:"The fatal blow was so violent that this outgrowth went all to pieces."};
descriptions["18445"]={cn:"魔针布满的刺让你的对手闻风丧胆。",en:"Despite its mortal qualities, a simple flourish of this needle is all it takes to scare your target stiff. Only its owner is immune to its portal."};
descriptions["18446"]={cn:"新型多功能武器，你值得拥有。",en:"Once you\'ve mastered this ring, the energy that binds it to its bearer means it can be also used as a boomerang."};
descriptions["18447"]={cn:"魔杖一出，严冬将至。请勿在熊孩子面前使用。",en:"When you stick this staff violently in the ground, all the creatures in the nearby area fall asleep. However, we don\'t advise you use it around children."};
descriptions["18448"]={cn:"旧卡扔出去，新卡补进来。加以练习，削铁如泥。",en:"When these cards are cast, new ones will immediately appear in the hands of their owner. With practice, you will also be able to use them to slice your enemies into little slivers."};
descriptions["18449"]={cn:"由壶枢的口水粘合而成，可以贯穿最坚硬的护甲。",en:"Able to pierce through even the most resistant armour, his blade is formed from two blocks held together by Victus\'s own saliva."};
descriptions["18450"]={cn:"非常有技术含量的武器，在魔之界打猎的猎人经常用它。",en:"A real tactical throw weapon, the hunters use it when hunting in the Shustuft Crust."};
descriptions["18451"]={cn:"这把法杖非常沉重，巨大的重量让那些愚蠢的冒险者望而却步。当然用来赶滋滋就有点过了。",en:"As heavy as it is imposing, this great mass will put off all but the most foolhardy of adventurers. However, Moskito hunting could be little taxing."};
descriptions["18452"]={cn:"当身处险境时，这柄魔之剑会舍弃防御，释放邪恶的本体，给敌人带来噩梦般得痛苦。",en:"Once it\'s been stuck in an enemy, the protection attached to the sword will come off, unleashing an evil Shushu that will petrify the target with pain."};
descriptions["18453"]={cn:"轻薄锋利，便于使用。宝藏猎人甚至用它来劈开矿脉。",en:"Lightly built, this is the ideal axe to chop everything that moves into smithereens. It is so resistant, some Enutrofs even use to cut through rocks when they\'re mining for precious stones."};
descriptions["18454"]={cn:"魔锤一出，谁与争锋。抓鱼摘果，无所不能。",en:"Those who have noticed the shock wave that is emitted with each hit don\'t tend to live long enough to tell the tale. But some of the cleverer observers also use it for collecting fruit from trees and fishing."};
descriptions["18456"]={cn:"挖个坑给对手跳，不大不小刚刚好。",en:"Useful for digging the graves of your enemies, just the site of this shovel is sometimes enough to make your enemies dig their own."};
descriptions["18457"]={cn:"可鄙的时装，按您的灵魂量身定制。",en:"A despicable costume tailored to your soul."};
descriptions["18458"]={cn:"谁都希望一整天的心情都是暖暖的。这件胸甲能让你从内而外感到温暖，你值得拥有。",en:"Who hasn\'t dreamed of one day of warming the cockles of their heart? Now, with this breastplate that warms you up from the inside out, you can."};
descriptions["18459"]={cn:"魔族的这部分原来经常被用作门挡。后来有人觉得做成一顶帽子会更好。",en:"Intact, this half of a Shushu is usually used as a door stop. Then some people decided it would make a better hat."};
descriptions["18460"]={cn:"曾经装备了这个披风的人会隐形。如今只能在布拉克玛旅馆的地毯上看见它了。",en:"There was once a time when this cape made its wearer invisible. Nowadays, it\'s merely used to decorate the floors of Brakmar\'s taverns."};
descriptions["18461"]={cn:"据说装备了这个肩甲的人都已经成了受害者。你会是下一个吗？",en:"It is said that the protections that adorn these shoulder have already made victims of their own. Will you be next?"};
descriptions["18462"]={cn:"园丁必备，在播种之前可以用这种鞋子在地上挖坑。",en:"Ideal for gardeners, these boots are used to dig holes in the ground before planting seedlings in them."};
descriptions["18463"]={cn:"虽然这枚戒指蕴含着巨大的力量，但持有者会因为一股奇怪的力量变得非常易怒。一定有办法能破除这个魔咒。",en:"Despite the power contained in this ring, its bearer remains bridled by a strange force. There must surely be a way to break the evil spell."};
descriptions["18464"]={cn:"魔眼的残留嵌入了这个护符，戴上它的人会在每场战斗之前获得一个强力的光环。",en:"Flaxhid\'s remains encrusted into this Talisman give off an aura of power that adorns its bearer before each combat."};
descriptions["18465"]={cn:"树枝可以在布拉克玛茁壮成长。",en:"This cutting takes well when planted in Brakmar soil."};
descriptions["18466"]={cn:"栽下松树枝，慢慢可以拥有整片松树林。",en:"With this cutting, you can usher in an age of Pines."};
descriptions["18467"]={cn:"坚硬、强韧，充满了樱桃的香气。",en:"Elderberry Wood contains a concentrated poison deep in its bark."};
descriptions["18468"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["18469"]={cn:"要还是不要？一不小心就会陷入踌躇不决之中。",en:"Wood you, or wood you not? This wood would make you indecisive if you weren\'t careful!"};
descriptions["18470"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["18471"]={cn:"可能被某人坐在屁股下很久了。",en:"This seed has probably been sitting at the bottom of someone\'s pocket for too long."};
descriptions["18472"]={cn:"金银花种子能在埃努卓神域茁壮成长。",en:"This seed takes well when planted in Enurado soil."};
descriptions["18473"]={cn:"适量使用，虽然很好吃，但是会让你的胸毛疯狂生长。",en:"Use sparingly when cooking. It might taste delicious, but it will put hairs on your chest at a devastating rate."};
descriptions["18474"]={cn:"金银花朵适合干燥和金光闪闪的土壤。",en:"Kamamile Flowers like dry and kama-rich earths."};
descriptions["18475"]={cn:"据说安妮丽莎之神用它来做面膜。",en:"It is believed the goddess Eniripsa herself used this herb to make a skin cream."};
descriptions["18476"]={cn:"作为财富的象征，在上流社会经常被当作装饰。",en:"This flower is often used as a symbol of wealth in high society vases."};
descriptions["18477"]={cn:"埋下种子，收获纯天然的菜花。",en:"Plant this seed to grow your very own Jollyflower."};
descriptions["18478"]={cn:"向日葵种子有益健康，让人心情愉快、容光焕发。",en:"Sunflower Seeds are very good for your health, and will make you blossom with happiness!"};
descriptions["18479"]={cn:"菜花对人体有益...多吃点，能让你恢复青春！",en:"Jollyflowers are very good for you - eat some and you\'ll get your second wind in no time!"};
descriptions["18480"]={cn:"花菜中的绿巨人：特大花菜！",en:"It\'s the jolly green giant of the vegetable world: the Jumbo Jollyflower!"};
descriptions["18481"]={cn:"这种花一直以来是文森特先生的标志。有一天他独自出门去寻找这种花，之后就再也没有回来...",en:"This flower has long been the emblem of Vince Van Gode, who dedicated several works to it. His meeting with a wild specimen in full flower was fatal..."};
descriptions["18482"]={cn:"一种油性的花卉，可以用来制作上等的沐浴露。",en:"This slightly oily sunflower does wonders for your hair and skin."};
descriptions["18483"]={cn:"致密的蓝宝石，闪耀着神秘的光芒...也许只是一个倒影。",en:"This intense blue gem seems to glow with a mysterious and mystical energy... unless that\'s just a reflection."};
descriptions["18484"]={cn:"这颗蓝宝石宁可一直这样暗淡着，这样它就可以避免被人发现而在戒指或者手镯上慵懒度日了。",en:"This sapphire is rather dull, which means it can spend days and days on a ring or bracelet before anyone even notices it."};
descriptions["18485"]={cn:"这种具备抗震性能的金属经常被用来制造盾牌和盔甲。",en:"This shock-resistant metal is often used to make shields and armor."};
descriptions["18486"]={cn:"一旦这种金属被制造成武器，它的敌人只能感叹自己命运不济了。",en:"Once this titanium has been transformed into a weapon, it\'ll be able to tell its victims how life really is, for real."};
descriptions["18487"]={cn:"自然界每天都有奇迹发生，比如这条鱼，它出生的时候一定是脸先着地了...",en:"Nature is sometimes capable of wonders. In this case, the mother fell flat on her face..."};
descriptions["18488"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["18489"]={cn:"这条鱼可以成为敲打钉子的完美工具。",en:"A fish that will make a perfect tool for hammering nails."};
descriptions["18490"]={cn:"不要小看它，它会发飙的...",en:"When called common, this shark turns red with anger..."};
descriptions["18491"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few drops should suffice."};
descriptions["18492"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few drops should suffice."};
descriptions["18493"]={cn:"这皮真的没什么存在感。",en:"If you\'re not paying attention to this skin, you might even forget it exists."};
descriptions["18494"]={cn:"蒸汽生皮是在怪物弥留之际才能获得，稍不留神就消失得无影无踪。",en:"Steamy Skin is collected during a last breath. It doesn\'t stay on a monster very long, and vanishes in the blink of an eye."};
descriptions["18495"]={cn:"滴着黄金般的液体，混入了些许卡玛颜料。",en:"This slobber drools in golden strands. Light kama pigments are mixed into this slimy liquid."};
descriptions["18496"]={cn:"80%是由融化的黄金制成。女人们都把它当作奢侈品，非常抢手。",en:"This slobber is made from 80% molten gold. It is very sought-after by women who consider it to be a luxury item."};
descriptions["18497"]={cn:"纪念你在972年的达图拉大赛中勇夺胜利。",en:"You earned this title because of your victory in the Dathuriades of 972."};
descriptions["18498"]={cn:"点击两下来把整组古代资源转换成新的资源。古代资源需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
