descriptions["18516"]={cn:"来自斯拉姆神域的骨头。你在十二世界绝对找不到这样的东西。",en:"A strange bone from the Sram Dimension. You won\'t find anything similar in the World of Twelve."};
descriptions["18517"]={cn:"具有较强的腐蚀性，在斯拉姆神域常被用于制作毒药。",en:"This substance is rather corrosive, and might be used in the creation of poisons in Srambad."};
descriptions["18518"]={cn:"点击两下来把整组古代资源转换成新的资源。古代资源需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["18519"]={cn:"腐魂的骨头并非固体或液体，是由一种无法形容的物质形成的。只有在一瞬间才能收集得到。",en:"Solkrupt\'s bones are not solid or liquid, but are made of an undescribable matter than can still be grasped for a short moment."};
descriptions["18520"]={cn:"就像你的鼻子一样必不可少。",en:"This Lock stands out like the nose on your face. You can\'t miss it."};
descriptions["18521"]={cn:"点击两下来把整组古代资源转换成新的资源。古代资源需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["18522"]={cn:"动感搁板给了埃努卓宝箱们生命来预防小偷。",en:"Animated shelfs allow Enurado chests to come to life and defend the dimension from thieves."};
descriptions["18523"]={cn:"这些代表着财富的搭扣在埃努卓神域四处可见。",en:"The Gildings are carved all over the Enotrof god\'s dimension. They are a symbol of wealth."};
descriptions["18524"]={cn:"这个护符散发着其穿戴者满满的恶意。",en:"This amulet emits all its previous wearer\'s evil."};
descriptions["18525"]={cn:"用来训练小死灵犬。每当它们开心的时候就会释放出一股电流刺激它们。",en:"This collar is used on young Dwarf Bulldaggers to train them as quickly as possibly. It shocks them with a jolt of electricity each time they express joy."};
descriptions["18526"]={cn:"“戴着这个护符让大家都知道你穷得只剩钱了。”",en:"\"It is by wearing your luck for all to see that you can become richer than rich.\""};
descriptions["18527"]={cn:"只有真正诚实和慷慨的人才配得上这个护符。但那些想混入上流社会的小偷往往也会佩戴。",en:"This amulet is offered to those who remain honest and generous regardless of the situation. But it is also worn by thieves who want to blend in with high society."};
descriptions["18528"]={cn:"悄无声息地从侧面给敌人一击。",en:"The shoulder pads allow you to discreetly hit your target in the sides."};
descriptions["18529"]={cn:"在白天会帮游荡的灵魂遮光，听说有时候手臂会不由自主地移动，不要在意。",en:"Thes shoulder pads protect wandering souls from the light of day. Don\'t be surprised if your arms sometimes move by themselves."};
descriptions["18530"]={cn:"这件护肩能够轻易吞下你的影子，据说甚至还能吞噬你附近的影子。",en:"These shoulder pads are large enough to swallow your shadow and be the only visitble thing. They\'re even said to swallow nearby shadows."};
descriptions["18531"]={cn:"“感受到了吝啬鬼深深的恶意。”",en:"\"Miser\'s shoulders carry kamas and a deep comtempt.\""};
descriptions["18532"]={cn:"斯拉姆面具能完美地隐藏你的身份，在这个城镇还是强烈推荐的。",en:"The Srambad Mask lets you hide your identity, which is highly recommended in this town."};
descriptions["18533"]={cn:"戴上这个头盔让你看上去跟腐魂一样空虚和黑暗。可别迷失了自我！",en:"If you wear this mask, you\'ll look as empty and dark as Solkrupt. Make sure you don\'t lose sight of your true identity!"};
descriptions["18534"]={cn:"可以抵挡头部遭受的物理伤害，但是不能抵挡噪音和气味伤害，也不能保证你在战斗中能看得清楚。",en:"He partly covers your head\'s damages and interest. But he doesn\'t cover acoustic and collateral damage, and doesn\'t guarantee good visibility during combat."};
descriptions["18535"]={cn:"这个胸甲会挤压你的胸部让你痛苦不堪，但是这一切都是值得的。",en:"This chest plate will constrict your chest till you cry, but the bonuses it offers are well worth the pain."};
descriptions["18536"]={cn:"这件胸甲是由一种从腐魂体内提取出来的材料制成的。它会吞噬你的皮肤表面以便和你的骨骼融合，从而提升你的防御力。",en:"This chest plate is made of a material extracted from Solkrupt. It devours the surface of your skin to better fuse with your skeleton and offer better protection."};
descriptions["18537"]={cn:"这件胸甲吞噬主人的灵魂，让他失去七情六欲。",en:"This breast plate eats its wearer\'s soul to make him completely immune to blows and emotions."};
descriptions["18538"]={cn:"“卡玛以人为本。”",en:"\"He who borrows to build Kama muscles, builds to sell better.\""};
descriptions["18539"]={cn:"请再三确认是否锁上并系紧腰带，否则等钱包被偷了可别抱怨。",en:"Triple check that you\'ve closed and tightened your belt. If that\'s not the case, don\'t complain when your kama-laden purses are stolen."};
descriptions["18540"]={cn:"这件披风会揭露你最黑暗的一面，让你不再见光死。",en:"This cloak unveils your darkest side and protects your other side from the light."};
descriptions["18541"]={cn:"让你在深夜中悄无声息。",en:"A stealthy cloak that allows you to melt into the dark, dark night."};
descriptions["18542"]={cn:"一件有用的斗篷，带有口袋，可以装下最可怕的易爆液体和火焰瓶！",en:"A useful cloak with pockets for the most terrifying explosive potions and cocktails!"};
descriptions["18543"]={cn:"想穿多久穿多久，当然前提是你要按时付钱。",en:"This cloak can be worn for as long as you like, on condition that you\'re happy to pay interest on it by the required due date."};
descriptions["18544"]={cn:"穿上它你就会天天哆嗦，真好。",en:"This cloak makes you even more honest than you already are, and that\'s never a bad thing."};
descriptions["18545"]={cn:"据说一位无名的神偷被一根腰带勒死了。在临终前，他笑得像个疯子一样。",en:"A famous thief, whose name we don\'t know, was allegedly accidentally stranged by a belt. Right before the end, he is said to have started laughing like a madman."};
descriptions["18546"]={cn:"穿上之后腰身马上小一圈。",en:"This belt squeezes your waist so much that it shrinks it."};
descriptions["18547"]={cn:"“对于那些勒紧裤腰带才能满足需求的人，信用是唯一的财富。”",en:"\"Credit is only the apparent wealth of those who tighten their belts to meet their needs.\""};
descriptions["18548"]={cn:"防震腰带吸收并分散受到的伤害，或者也可能会瞬间瓦解，功亏一篑。",en:"The Schock Absorber can spread out damage over time, or can result in a premature termination of the contract, which results in the immediate loss of all means."};
descriptions["18549"]={cn:"请按时穿戴这根腰带，否则它会让你知道什么叫利息！",en:"If you don\'t wear this belt regularly, it will let you know about it with interest!"};
descriptions["18550"]={cn:"有了这双鞋，倒立着走都没关系。",en:"With these boots, walk with your head down in Sram\'s shadow!"};
descriptions["18551"]={cn:"穿上这双鞋，腐魂更难找到你了。当然，不用多久他就会发现其实有人在跟踪他。",en:"By wearing his boots, Solkrupt will have a much harder time finding you! Well, after a few moments, he\'ll know that someone is following him."};
descriptions["18552"]={cn:"对透支的敌人产生滞纳金和利息。乔基最擅长计算和钱有关的数学题了。",en:"Agiots cause damage and interest when an enemy is overdrawn, and are calculated depending on the damage plus interests."};
descriptions["18553"]={cn:"埃努卓神域出品的一种密码锁，给你的宝箱添加额外的安全保护。我不会告诉你其实密码被刻在了宝箱里的一枚卡玛上。",en:"This ring is of Enurado design. You can use it to add an extra layer of protection to your chest, thanks to a code engraved in the Kamas that you keep hidden away from covetous gazes."};
descriptions["18554"]={cn:"一旦戴上这个指环，它就会帮你标记出重要债务的截止日期。",en:"From the moment you put this ring on, you\'re going to have to do something and it will mark the end of an important era for you."};
descriptions["18555"]={cn:"牢牢锁住你的钥匙，紧握在手，天下我有。",en:"The perfect tool to keep track of your keys and always have them to hand."};
descriptions["18556"]={cn:"据说这把匕首和斯拉姆神的那把同款，不过应该只是某些铁匠的营销手段罢了。",en:"This dagger was allegedly forged from two longblades belonging to the god Sram, but that\'s just some legend invented by the blacksmith so his weapon would sell better."};
descriptions["18557"]={cn:"湿伯是族人中最厉害的那个。四只手臂给予了他巨大的力量和速度。",en:"Nataraja is one of his Eminence\'s favourite races. Its fours arms give it a fearsome strength and speed."};
descriptions["18558"]={cn:"据说刀刃在没有星星和月亮的夜晚会变得格外锋利。当然这只是一个传说，那么暗谁看得清楚啊。",en:"This blade is said to be sharper on starless and moonless nights. But it\'s just a rumor, as it\'s too dark to notice anything."};
descriptions["18559"]={cn:"这块墓碑一样的盾牌完全覆盖了手臂，难道这就是所谓的废物利用？",en:"This dome-shaped shield completely covers the arm. Could it be a gravestone recycled into a defensive weapon?"};
descriptions["18560"]={cn:"因为这把镰刀的刀刃酷似笑脸，让使用者每次打中敌人或队友时都不禁发笑。",en:"This scythe\'s blade is said to look like a smile, and makes its user smile himself everytime he hits a friend or a foe!"};
descriptions["18561"]={cn:"刚在十二世界亮相就已被广泛使用。现在你可以不用去银行抢现金，直接抢别人的卡就可以了。",en:"Having only recently made its appearance in the World of Twelve, it is now widely in use. Now you can get Kamas out of just about anyone, without having to go to the bank."};
descriptions["18562"]={cn:"透支金铲可以用来立即还清债务或者继续透支下去。",en:"The Overdrawn allows for debts to be settled or damage to be dealt over time."};
descriptions["18563"]={cn:"指针的效果变幻莫测，取决于前来提款的是你，还是你的对手。",en:"The penalties caused by this hand are not always the same, depending on whether or not the withdrawal is made from an opponent other than your own."};
descriptions["18564"]={cn:"从未有小偷能对其造成任何凹痕，常用于保护埃努卓神域的宝箱。",en:"No thief has ever managed to make a dent in this armor used to secure Enurado\'s chests."};
descriptions["18565"]={cn:"你的账户就靠这把钥匙保护了，除非你想把你的财产分一点出来。",en:"Your accounts are kept under lock and key, until you decide to come and withdraw some of your meager savings."};
descriptions["18566"]={cn:"在漫长的战斗进入尾声之时才会体现出价值，等待机会，给出致命的一击。",en:"This sword shows its true worth at the end of combat. It allows for attacks with a high damage output, waiting for a critical hit."};
descriptions["18567"]={cn:"这把铲子借给你的前提是你得在有生之年收集一笔巨大的财产。",en:"This shovel is loaned out to you on the condition that you gather an immense amount of Kamas during your lifetime."};
descriptions["18568"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["18569"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["18570"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["18571"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["18572"]={cn:"闻着臭，吃着香！",en:"Srambad Bread is rather tasty, if you can get over the smell and look of it."};
descriptions["18573"]={cn:"带着一股淡淡的杏仁味。奸商们都对此特别敏感，因为有些毒药也有相同的味道。",en:"This bread has a faint taste of almonds. Rich merchants are wary of it as some poisons have the same smell."};
descriptions["18574"]={cn:"这酸爽的滋味让你根本停不下来。",en:"This sweet and sour dish tasts like fat and bone."};
descriptions["18575"]={cn:"无法忍受的味道，让你臭气熏天。",en:"This potion tastes disgusting and gives you bad breath."};
descriptions["18576"]={cn:"真是难以下咽的食物，只有吝啬鬼才能发现它真正的价值。",en:"This garbage-tasting dish is a culinary curiosity that many misers appreciate for its true value."};
descriptions["18577"]={cn:"让你变成真男人，丝毫不怕疼痛。",en:"This potion turns you into a real tank and makes you almost immune to pain."};
descriptions["18578"]={cn:"在欺诈街道非常受欢迎，只有斯拉姆神域中的有钱人才会有，你可以借一个来...",en:"This item is very popular in the Trickree neighbourhood. Only the richest people in Srambad have one. Unless you manage to make a passable counterfeit."};
descriptions["18579"]={cn:"一个能带来天堂般财富的漂亮盆栽。",en:"A pretty plant attracting wealth and prosperity to the Havens."};
descriptions["18580"]={cn:"潘朵拉用来从强大怪物（130至150级）身上收集创生力的便携式机器。",en:"This portable little machine was created by Pandora to harvest Wakfu from powerful monsters (Lvl. 130 to 150)."};
descriptions["18581"]={cn:"这个由潘朵拉制造的便携式机器能够从强大的怪物身上收集创生力。",en:"This portable machine created by Pandora allows for the gathering of Wakfu from powerful monsters."};
descriptions["18582"]={cn:"便携式次元同步传送器，能在同一次元内进行短距离的传送。",en:"\"Individual-Dimensional-Syncroportal\". This machine is used to travel short distances within a dimension."};
descriptions["18583"]={cn:"非常实用的障碍物。堵在庇护袋门口，别人再也进不来了。",en:"Quite practical and useful for sealing forbidden passages, protecting your Haven Bag from unwanted visitors, or even for use as a pillow."};
descriptions["18584"]={cn:"光彩照人，温暖你心。",en:"A magnificent and authentic lamp cut from a magnificent and authentic Ohwymi cactus. It\'ll warm your heart!"};
descriptions["18585"]={cn:"源自蘑菇地的潮湿地表。本来没有照明功能，不过现在涂过萨迪达防腐剂啦！",en:"These mushrooms come from the moist ground in the Fungopole. Normally they can\'t handle light, but they\'ve been treated by a Sadida preservative."};
descriptions["18586"]={cn:"像踩在湿答答的浴室防滑垫上，感觉好不好只有你知道了。",en:"You\'ll feel like you\'re walking on a wet bathmat - it\'s left to you to decide if that\'s a good thing."};
descriptions["18587"]={cn:"美丽记忆，永久珍藏。",en:"A nice trophy for your personal collection."};
descriptions["18588"]={cn:"美丽记忆，永久珍藏。",en:"A nice trophy for your personal collection."};
descriptions["18589"]={cn:"美丽记忆，永久珍藏。",en:"A nice trophy for your personal collection."};
descriptions["18590"]={cn:"美丽记忆，永久珍藏。",en:"A nice trophy for your personal collection."};
descriptions["18591"]={cn:"便携式次元同步传送器，能在已被记录的次元之间任意传送以及激活次元锚点。",en:"\"Individual-Dimensional-Syncroportal\". This machine is used to travel between those dimensions whose coordinates have been recorded, and to activate dimensional anchors."};
descriptions["18592"]={cn:"送给那些咸猪手。",en:"For those who think the best place to keep your hands is in pockets."};
descriptions["18593"]={cn:"送给那些目光长远的人。",en:"For those who can see the bigger picture."};
descriptions["18594"]={cn:"有些人可不怕弄脏他们的手。",en:"For those who aren\'t afraid of taking the low road."};
descriptions["18595"]={cn:"在欺诈街道非常受欢迎，只有斯拉姆神域中的有钱人才会有。",en:"This item is very popular in the Trickree neighbourhood. Only the richest people in Srambad have one."};
descriptions["18596"]={cn:"虽然这是斯拉姆神域最常见的物品，但这把匕首是独一无二的。它被一层特殊的材质覆盖着。",en:"The dagger is the most common item in Srambad, but this one is special. It is covered in a very special material."};
descriptions["18597"]={cn:"你已经获得了无数价值连城的好东西。",en:"You have got away with plenty of nice items that can be sold to the highest bidder."};
descriptions["18598"]={cn:"当今斯拉姆神域的流通货币。",en:"The Skrama is the currency used in Srambad, the dimension of the Sram god."};
descriptions["18599"]={cn:"含有致命毒药，一滴足以让你升天。",en:"This small bottle contains a deadly poison, a single drop of which would send you straight to the grave."};
descriptions["18600"]={cn:"可以进入斯拉姆储藏室。",en:"This key gives you access to the Srambad Stockroom."};
descriptions["18601"]={cn:"无须去银行，绿色通道让你直达埃努卓神域。",en:"This pass lets you travel to the god Enutrof\'s Dimension without needing to go to the bank."};
descriptions["18602"]={cn:"一个恐怖的雕像，适合喜欢潜行和背刺的人。",en:"A terrifying statue for lovers of shadows and backstabs."};
descriptions["18603"]={cn:"贪婪的眼神注视着你。",en:"A statue with a greedy look on its face."};
descriptions["18604"]={cn:"你必须得搞清楚你的导师想说些什么...",en:"You really have to wonder if your guidance counselor really knew what they were talking about..."};
descriptions["18605"]={cn:"这个佣兵将于您的帐号绑定，陪您共同作战。注意：除非特殊情况，使用之后将无法撤销。",en:"This item enables you to link this sidekick to your account and use it in combat. Careful! This action cannot be undone, except under certain circumstances."};
descriptions["18606"]={cn:"你可以将助手绑定至你的账号并在战斗中使用。注意！除去个别特殊情况，这项操作无法被取消。",en:"This item enables you to link this sidekick to your account and use it in combat. Careful! This action cannot be undone, except under certain circumstances."};
descriptions["18607"]={cn:"来一起洗个澡吧！",en:"Once cast on someone, they\'re sure to get a shower."};
descriptions["18608"]={cn:"水节上最好的装扮！",en:"The perfect costume to celebrate the Water Festival!"};
descriptions["18610"]={cn:"为了弥补你脸蛋的先天缺陷，我们授予你这个称号。",en:"You won this title for the absolute lack of redeeming qualities your face possesses."};
descriptions["18612"]={cn:"能力越大，责任越大。",en:"With great power comes great responsibility."};
descriptions["18615"]={cn:"适合不羁放荡穿越时空的你。",en:"Just the outfit you need for transitioning between your different lives."};
descriptions["18616"]={cn:"穿着这件时装，你就获得了在关键时刻保持冷静的能力。千万不要慌！",en:"With this costume on, you should be able to keep a cool head, even in emergencies. Make sure you don\'t lose your nerve!"};
descriptions["18617"]={cn:"作为一名冒险者，要时刻准备踏上征程。",en:"You need to be ready for adventure at all times, right? I rest my case."};
descriptions["18618"]={cn:"放在庇护袋的显要位置，让客人们眼红吧！",en:"A pretty trophy to put on your mantlepiece and proudly show to all your friends."};
descriptions["18619"]={cn:"专为那些匆匆而过的人设计的概念包包。",en:"An ideal bag for the adventurer who\'s just passin\' through."};
descriptions["18620"]={cn:"采用最前沿的尖端科技。实用而宽敞，唯一的缺陷是重量。",en:"This bag is at the forefront of technomagic. Practical and quite spacious, its only downfall is its weight."};
descriptions["18621"]={cn:"这个称号用来纪念你周游十二世界的旅行。",en:"This title is a reflection of your travels throughout the World of Twelve."};
descriptions["18622"]={cn:"这个称号代表你参加过蒸汽冒险。",en:"This title symbolizes your participation in the Steam adventure."};
descriptions["18623"]={cn:"纪念你在972年的格鲁大赛中勇夺胜利。",en:"You earned this title after winning the Gelu\'Mode 972!"};
descriptions["18628"]={cn:"一本记满了关于龙鸟的故事书。",en:"This storybook is all about dragoturkeys."};
descriptions["18629"]={cn:"一本记满了龙鸟食谱的书。",en:"A recipe book full of Dragoturkey recipes."};
descriptions["18630"]={cn:"一本完整的龙鸟教科书，教你具体应该如何给龙鸟套上轭具以及上鞍。",en:"An accurate and unabridged book that will explain, in detail, how to harness and saddle your dragoturkey mount."};
descriptions["18631"]={cn:"龙鸟的鞍和缰绳",en:"A Saddle and Reins for a dragoturkey"};
descriptions["18632"]={cn:"所有的黑疯兔地洞为你开启，其实也没几个。",en:"This cloak will open the doors of all the Black Wabbit burrows to you, not that there are many of them."};
descriptions["18633"]={cn:"据说这把剑是由一种蔬菜制成的，食用这种蔬菜能让人的肌肉变得很发达。",en:"It is said that this sword was made of a vegetable that is renowned for giving big muscles to people who eat it."};
descriptions["18634"]={cn:"献给最棒的胡萝卜汁制造者。",en:"A ring entrusted to the best traditional Cawotte juice makers."};
descriptions["18635"]={cn:"强大伟岸的福狸光曾把这枚戒指赠予了他心怡的女神，直到他遇到了另一个女神。",en:"The strong and mighty Lenaldix once offered this superb ring to one of his conquests, before asking for it back to give to the next."};
descriptions["18636"]={cn:"僵尸铲上都是刺，想要运用自如就得戴上这种手套。",en:"The Zombo is covered with splinters, so it\'s necessary to wear these gloves if you want to dance with it successfully."};
descriptions["18637"]={cn:"最棒的兔守卫才能获得。有没有搞错！",en:"This amulet is usually awarded to excellent Wabbit Guawds.  They must have made a mistake."};
descriptions["18638"]={cn:"当兔诸侯进入一个只有他才能进入的地方时才会佩戴这个虎符。它能吸收臭味。",en:"This amulet is worn by the Emiw when he goes to answer nature\'s call. It is said to absorb bad smells."};
descriptions["18639"]={cn:"在旺博戴上标志性的头带之前，他一直戴着这个护符。",en:"Before wearing his trademark bandana, Wambo proudly wore this amulet in public."};
descriptions["18640"]={cn:"僵尸兔粑粑在净化仪式中穿戴的腰带。目测要火！",en:"A belt worn by Wo Zwombbits during puwification rituals. It\'s no surprise that they never became popular."};
descriptions["18641"]={cn:"全进口胡萝卜纯手工打造，无论女汉子夏天食用还是软妹子冬天自用，都是最棒的体验。",en:"The Lenald Walm Pelt is made entirely of Cawotte. It keeps you warm in the winter and is still delicious when next summer comes around."};
descriptions["18642"]={cn:"据说这个头盔是用来防止病毒的。百密必有一疏，将就着用吧。",en:"This helm is said to protect against viwuses. It\'s not the ultimate protection, but it\'s better than nothing."};
descriptions["18643"]={cn:"据说是机械兔首领某天晚上和兔皇帝在一起的时候穿的鞋子。",en:"It\'s said the the Chief of Wobots himself wore these boots during an evening with the Wa Wabbit."};
descriptions["18644"]={cn:"兔皇帝见福狸的时候穿的护肩。",en:"The Wa Wabbit wore these shoulder pads when they went to war with the Lenalds."};
descriptions["18645"]={cn:"疯兔大元老能预见未来，这把武器更能让他锦上添花。",en:"The Grand Viziw Wabbit can always see a few moves ahead, and this dagger lets him use that skill to pewfection."};
descriptions["18646"]={cn:"这份文件授予你\"972年奥古幸存者\"称号。",en:"This document allows you to claim the title of Survivor of the Ogrest Games 972."};
descriptions["18647"]={cn:"收集100块碎片，合成噬魂胸甲。",en:"100 of these fragments must be collected to create a Souleater Breastplate."};
descriptions["18648"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few drops should suffice."};
descriptions["18666"]={cn:"收集100个碎片，合成千足金钥匙圈。",en:"Collect 100 of these fragments to create a Golden Keychain."};
