descriptions["18765"]={cn:"GA\n莱昂纳尔，四个人中最严肃最强壮的那个。",en:"\"GA\"\nLeonael, the most serious and strongest of the four."};
descriptions["18766"]={cn:"佣兵就必须保护好自己的身体和灵魂。",en:"A mercenary must protect his body and soul."};
descriptions["18767"]={cn:"奥古狂热成员从佣兵仓库偷出来的靴子。",en:"These boots were stolen from the Mercenary Reserve by members of Ogrest\'s Cult."};
descriptions["18768"]={cn:"一个合格的佣兵必须保护好自己的后背。",en:"A good mercenary must always protect his behind."};
descriptions["18769"]={cn:"两截棍是唐纳朗基罗最喜欢的武器。没有武器，他就无法为下水道的安全而战斗！",en:"The Nun Chukapi is Donalangelo\'s preferred weapon. Without this unified weapon, he can\'t fight as hard as he\'ll need to enforce peace in the sewers!"};
