descriptions["18771"]={cn:"这个护符是由变异粘胶和独行虫孵化后茧的残留制成的。",en:"This amulet is made from Larva Mucus and the remains of cocoons after Larvae have hatched."};
descriptions["18773"]={cn:"捏一捏，放点料，推进去，烤一烤。粘粘的披萨，好吃的披萨。",en:"Knead the larva the right way. Garnish it with the best ingredients you have. Bake it in the oven for a few seconds. Voila! It\'s a bit sticky, but plenty tasty!"};
descriptions["18774"]={cn:"佣兵随时肩负着重任。",en:"A mercenary is always ready to shoulder a burden."};
descriptions["18775"]={cn:"可爱的模型，用于装饰小屋。",en:"A lovely vault for your personal decoration."};
descriptions["18776"]={cn:"能力越大，责任越大，把柄越多...",en:"The power to defend the week is a great strength, but also a great weakness."};
descriptions["18779"]={cn:"皮革是物品制作中的理想原料。通过10级皮匠制作，可用于21-35级装备等用品制作。",en:"This raw leather is one of your first refinements."};
descriptions["18780"]={cn:"丝线是物品制作中的理想原料。通过0级草药制作，可用于0-20级装备等用品制作。",en:"This string isn\'t really useful for anything, but has the advantage of being easy to put away and thus be forgotten forever."};
