descriptions["18893"]={cn:"收集100块碎片，合成黑暗弗拉德肩甲。（帐号绑定）",en:"Collect 100 of these fragments to create a pair of Dark Vlad\'s Epaulettes (linked to the account)."};
descriptions["18894"]={cn:"这副肩甲久经沙场。虽然不如从前那么坚固，但是如果你不想武器报废的话，最好不要用力砍它。",en:"These epaulettes have seen more than one battle. They may not look too sturdy, but best not to hit them too hard if you want to keep your weapon."};
descriptions["18895"]={cn:"柔软的披风，可以不穿内衣贴身穿着！一种展现男子汉气概的优雅方式...",en:"This cape has a reputation for legendary softness, which means you can wear it without any underwear! An elegant way to expose yourself..."};
descriptions["18896"]={cn:"哈利是个很有智慧的老人，喜欢光着脚钓鱼。终于有一天，在某个漫长的夏日的傍晚，他把自己的靴子忘记在萨弗基亚的码头上了。",en:"Harry was an old wise man who loved to fish with bare feet. Inevitably, after a long summer day, he forgot his boots on the Sufokian docks."};
descriptions["18897"]={cn:"这面盾牌中含有海水的成分，让你在战斗中感觉清凉爽快，特别是女朋友没在边上观战的时候。",en:"This magnificent shield contains a few drops of seawater. Not only does it bring good luck but it can also be used as a flask."};
descriptions["18898"]={cn:"只有我，最摇摆！",en:"Gettin\' jiggly wit it!"};
descriptions["18899"]={cn:"这件胸甲吞噬主人的灵魂，让他失去七情六欲。",en:"This breast plate eats its wearer\'s soul to make him completely immune to blows and emotions."};
descriptions["18900"]={cn:"坠饰里流出美味粘稠的蜂蜜，但现在它看起来更像冰冻蜂蜜。放心，不会流得你全身，只会流到上半身。",en:"Sticky and delicious honey once flowed from this amulet, but now it looks more like iced honey. One thing is sure: it won\'t leak all over your torso."};
descriptions["18901"]={cn:"绑在你的手上，妈妈再也不用担心我会丢钥匙了。",en:"The perfect tool to keep track of your keys and always have them to hand."};
descriptions["18902"]={cn:"一场豪赌的产物，赢的那一方取走了这条闪亮的腰带。",en:"This magnificent belt is the result of a mad bet to restore one of the most beautiful belts ever created in Amakna: the Powerful Dazzling Belt! Pakape Promethe won the contest."};
descriptions["18903"]={cn:"曾经属于熊猫武僧首领张·冰雪美酒。因为缺少实验志愿者，他不得已只能自己来试用斗笠，测试它作为尿壶的隐藏功能。",en:"The Solomonk used to belong to an old Pandawa chief who was an expert in laxative potions. Lacking willing subjects, he had to test the potions himself, and used it as a chamber pot."};
descriptions["18904"]={cn:"魔眼的残留嵌入了这个护符，戴上它的人会在每场战斗之前获得一个强力的光环。",en:"Flaxhid\'s remains encrusted into this Talisman give off an aura of power that adorns its bearer before each combat."};
descriptions["18911"]={cn:"呃对，这是一把剑。呃不，不能借你用。",en:"YES, this is a sword. AND NO, it\'s not abused."};
