descriptions["19016"]={cn:"如果是你阿玛克纳的国民，用这张魔法卷轴会将你直接传送到阿玛克纳。",en:"This magical scroll will teleport you directly to Amakna if you are of that nation."};
descriptions["19017"]={cn:"如果是你邦塔的国民，用这张魔法卷轴会将你直接传送到邦塔。",en:"This magical scroll will teleport you directly to Bonta if you are of that nation."};
descriptions["19018"]={cn:"如果是你萨弗基亚的国民，用这张魔法卷轴会将你直接传送到萨弗基亚。",en:"This magical scroll will teleport you directly to Sufokia if you are of that nation."};
descriptions["19019"]={cn:"如果是你布拉克玛的国民，用这张魔法卷轴会将你直接传送到布拉克玛。",en:"This magical scroll will teleport you directly to Brakmar if you are of that nation."};
descriptions["19020"]={cn:"这张魔法卷轴会将你直接传送到你的国家（或阿斯图布）。",en:"This magical scroll will teleport you directly to your Nation (or to Astrub)."};
descriptions["19021"]={cn:"用这张魔法卷轴直接传送到阿斯图布。",en:"This magical scroll will teleport you directly to Astrub."};
descriptions["19022"]={cn:"用这张魔法卷轴直接传送到你最后绑定的凤凰碑。",en:"This magical scroll will teleport you to your last save point."};
descriptions["19023"]={cn:"你是我的小呀小苹朵。",en:"This Apitizing Potion will make you very Api!"};
descriptions["19024"]={cn:"这种美味的热狗能让你变成一只忠诚的小汪汪。",en:"This yummy Hot-Dog will turn you into a loyal little Bow Wow."};
descriptions["19025"]={cn:"喝下它，头重脚轻。",en:"Drink this and put your feet up!"};
descriptions["19026"]={cn:"这颗辛辣的糖果会把你变成逗逗龙。",en:"This spicy candy will turn you into a Dragoune."};
descriptions["19027"]={cn:"这种有嚼劲的糖能让你变成调皮的鬼司通。",en:"This chewing gum will turn you into a mischievous Ghast."};
descriptions["19029"]={cn:"吃过蝴蝶吗？",en:"Have you got butterflies in your stomach?"};
descriptions["19030"]={cn:"鲁贝克斯之剑将在你的庇护袋中占据重要的地位。",en:"This Rubilax Sword will have pride of place in your Haven Bag."};
descriptions["19031"]={cn:"一个漂亮的雕像，照亮你的庇护袋。",en:"A pretty statue to brighten up your Haven."};
descriptions["19032"]={cn:"能够存放足够你喝一辈子的熊猫佳酿。",en:"It can hold all the Bamboo Milk you need to stumble your way through life."};
descriptions["19033"]={cn:"庇护袋内拥有各种蒸汽技术，充满了毁灭的气息。",en:"A bag kitted out with state of the art Foggernaut technology, powered by Stasis."};
descriptions["19034"]={cn:"现在你的庇护袋里布满了跳蚤和毛球。这下你可爽了！",en:"Now you have a Haven Bag filled with fleas and hairballs. Lucky you!"};
descriptions["19035"]={cn:"把大自然带回家吧！",en:"A high quality Haven Bag to bring the outdoors indoors!"};
descriptions["19036"]={cn:"你肯定不是这个庇护袋的第一个主人，当然也不会是最后一个。",en:"You\'re certainly not the first owner of this peaceful safe haven, and you won\'t be the last, either."};
descriptions["19037"]={cn:"一根很长的棒子，用来做什么呢？",en:"It\'s amazing what you can do with just a stick"};
descriptions["19038"]={cn:"曾经属于一位来自太古时期的精英。",en:"This helmet has been a member of the elite since time immemorial."};
descriptions["19039"]={cn:"如果你相信世界末日，那这个护符会让你多活一会儿。",en:"If you believe in the end of time, this Bli-Birch can protect you for a little while longer."};
descriptions["19040"]={cn:"这件肩甲非常古老，受到光照可能就化为灰烬的。",en:"This pair of epaulettes is so old that they risk turning to dust when exposed to sunlight."};
descriptions["19041"]={cn:"这是一双能让你四处游荡来打发时间的皮靴。",en:"This is a practical pair of boots for meowandering through time."};
descriptions["19042"]={cn:"这根腰带能绑住许多东西，包括你的裤子。",en:"This belt can keep things up forever, even your trousers."};
descriptions["19043"]={cn:"适合穿着去参加一场无尽的宴会。",en:"An ideal cloak to wear to banquets that go on and on and on."};
descriptions["19044"]={cn:"这件披风现在属于过去。",en:"This cloak now belongs to the past."};
descriptions["19045"]={cn:"又黑又硬的帽子。",en:"This ancient hat is solid as a rock!"};
descriptions["19046"]={cn:"这个胸甲完美地表现出你的复古感，让所有在阿玛克纳酒吧的宝藏猎人为其倾倒。",en:"This breastplate is the perfect accessory for your retro look. It will have the Enutrofettes in the Amakna Bar falling at your feet."};
descriptions["19047"]={cn:"穿上这双靴子，让你在当地人的眼里瞬间老了30岁。能让你很轻松地从年轻的时间法师身边走过去。",en:"With these boots on, you\'ll add thirty years to your age in the eyes of the local population. Which is great if you want to pass for a teenage Xelor."};
descriptions["19048"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["19049"]={cn:"这件胸甲风光不再。毋庸置疑，它现在只配得上这个名字。",en:"This breastplate has seen better days. There\'s no doubt about it, it\'s no longer of any use to an adventurer worthy of the name."};
descriptions["19050"]={cn:"格林戒指让我们想起了黑暗的过去。",en:"This Grim Ring reminds us of some of our darker days."};
descriptions["19051"]={cn:"一锤定音！",en:"So you can have a cracking start to your day!"};
descriptions["19052"]={cn:"去年的天气预报，你造吗？",en:"Perfect for predicting last year\'s weather."};
descriptions["19053"]={cn:"人人都有伤疤，背后都一个故事。",en:"Some actions leave scars. But they\'re often more worthwhile than they look."};
descriptions["19054"]={cn:"那些留下的记忆才是最重要的。",en:"The memory of those who have passed over is important to those left behind."};
descriptions["19055"]={cn:"心如止水，驱赶掉内心的邪念。",en:"Dark thoughts should be chased away by touching displays of affection."};
descriptions["19056"]={cn:"记忆是一个人最珍贵的财富，没有人能从你这儿抢走。",en:"A souvenir is the embodiment of a memory, and nobody should be able to take either of them away from you."};
descriptions["19057"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["19058"]={cn:"如果你想预测未来，最好带班作你的观众，能让他们慢点意识到你是一个大白痴。",en:"If you want to predict the future, it\'s best if you do it with class so your audience is so swept away with your smoke and mirrors that they don\'t notice what an idiot you are."};
descriptions["19059"]={cn:"穿上这件披风会成为同胞们的偶像，直到被他们暗杀...之前的主人看到你穿着这件披风一定很骄傲。",en:"Admired by all his compatriots until his assassination, your predecessor would be proud to see it on your shoulders."};
descriptions["19060"]={cn:"这把剑已经1000岁了，经历过10000场战斗，击败了100000个敌人。",en:"This thousand year old sword has seen ten thousand battles and defeated a hundred thousand opponents."};
descriptions["19061"]={cn:"真的很带感。",en:"It really is phenomenal."};
descriptions["19062"]={cn:"这件披风可遇而不可求，不过既然你已经穿上了说明也不是那么难以获得。",en:"This cloak may be the physical manifestation of luck itself, but the fact that you\'re wearing it wasn\'t left to chance."};
descriptions["19063"]={cn:"被无数伟大的战士穿着经过了时间的洗礼，一次都没有坏过。",en:"These boots have traveled through the ages on the feet of the proudest warriors, and they\'ve never once crumbled."};
descriptions["19064"]={cn:"比风更能飘，穿越时空飘啊飘。",en:"More lively than the wind, the Breath of Life travels through time to cut the lives of the living."};
descriptions["19065"]={cn:"这些古董碎片用于制造各种生活用具。",en:"These antique fragments are used to create numerous tools useful for everyday life."};
descriptions["19066"]={cn:"一种乐器的重要组成部分！",en:"The key part for a successful instrument!"};
descriptions["19067"]={cn:"点击两下来把整组古代资源转换成新的符文粉末。古代资源需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["19068"]={cn:"用来制作来自远古时期的装备。",en:"This fragment can be used to make the best protections from ancient times."};
descriptions["19069"]={cn:"前往地下城门口的兑奖机处兑换酷炫的奖励。",en:"Use the machine across from the dungeon to exchange your tokens for fantastic rewards."};
