descriptions["19093"]={cn:"带豆芙飞！",en:"A good strike with the Battofu is all you need to send these tofus packing."};
descriptions["19094"]={cn:"传说这把剪刀曾用于修剪熔岩绵球的毛。",en:"Legend has it that this blade was once used to cut down Gobbalrogs."};
descriptions["19095"]={cn:"一部分食谱在奥古之乱的时候遗失了。没人知道这到底是以喵喵为原料制成的还是喵喵的食物，后来大家投了票。最终决定喵布丁是由喵喵为原料制成的。",en:"Part of this recipe was lost during Ogrest\'s Chaos. Since nobody knew whether the Bow Meow was supposed to be the main ingredient, or whether this dish was actually meant for them to eat, they decided to organise a big competition. The result was that, from now on, the Bow Meow would be the main ingredient."};
descriptions["19096"]={cn:"阿斯图布最美味的料理之一。在邦塔的莎朗·莎姆王国内家喻户晓。",en:"One of the most delicate Astrubian specialities, Roast Crown of Piwi was a particular favourite at King Clustus Sheran Sharm\'s dinners in Bonta."};
descriptions["19097"]={cn:"至尊虫虫披萨是斯布林特的一个远房亲戚发明的。这绝对是厨师的噩梦，他从不按照常理出牌，经常随意更改配方。至尊虫虫披萨就是这么诞生的。",en:"Fhenrat is a distant cousin of the Sphincter Cell. He is a real pain in the neck for chefs, since he is never satisfied with the original recipes. He always wants them to leave something out or add an ingredient to the dishes they serve him. This Pizz\'larva is no exception to the rule."};
descriptions["19098"]={cn:"十二世界最流行的菜肴之一。每个地方都有独特的口味，但是阿玛克纳是最正宗的。",en:"Gobball Stew is one of the best known recipes in the World of Twelve. Each region has its own special take on it, and this is Amakna\'s version."};
descriptions["19099"]={cn:"十二世界最流行的菜肴之一。每个地方都有独特的口味，但是邦塔是最正宗的。",en:"Gobball Stew is one of the best known recipes in the World of Twelve. Each region has its own special take on it, and this is Bonta\'s version."};
descriptions["19100"]={cn:"十二世界最流行的菜肴之一。每个地方都有独特的口味，但是布拉克玛是最正宗的。",en:"Gobball Stew is one of the best known recipes in the World of Twelve. Each region has its own special take on it, and this is Brakmar\'s version."};
descriptions["19101"]={cn:"十二世界最流行的菜肴之一。每个地方都有独特的口味，但是萨弗基亚是最正宗的。",en:"Gobball Stew is one of the best known recipes in the World of Twelve. Each region has its own special take on it, and this is Sufokia\'s version."};
