descriptions["19103"]={cn:"十二世界最流行的菜肴之一。每个地方都有独特的口味，但是邦塔是最正宗的。",en:"Mashed Potatofu is one of the best known recipes in the World of Twelve. Each region has its own special take on it, and this is Bonta\'s version."};
descriptions["19104"]={cn:"十二世界最流行的菜肴之一。每个地方都有独特的口味，但是布拉克玛是最正宗的。",en:"Mashed Potatofu is one of the best known recipes in the World of Twelve. Each region has its own special take on it, and this is Brakmar\'s version."};
descriptions["19105"]={cn:"十二世界最流行的菜肴之一。每个地方都有独特的口味，但是萨弗基亚是最正宗的。",en:"Mashed Potatofu is one of the best known recipes in the World of Twelve. Each region has its own special take on it, and this is Sufokia\'s version."};
descriptions["19106"]={cn:"为了庆祝杜约成为拾贰月之神而在布拉克玛流传的民间美食。",en:"This national dish is a wintry treat that the Brakmarians share - a rare thing, indeed - on the 1st day of Djaul\'s month, Descendre."};
descriptions["19107"]={cn:"相传吉瓦曾经用邦塔风味汤诱惑了原来的壹月之神。",en:"Some claim this Bontarian dish was once used by Jiva to seduce Solar."};
descriptions["19108"]={cn:"营养丰富，足够一家人吃上好几个星期。作为阿玛克纳的经典菜肴经常出现在大胃王比赛的决赛。在968年拾壹月，一位参赛者连续吃了435个从而创造了最高纪录。从那以后，巨魔就被禁止参加这项赛事了。",en:"Extremely nutritious, one pot is enough to feed a family of six for 2 weeks. This Amaknian recipe is often used at finals of the biggest eater competitions. In Novamaire 968, the record was set at 435 pots downed by one of the competitors. Since then, Trools have been banned from the competitions."};
descriptions["19109"]={cn:"庆祝一位为了捕猎巨型爱鱿外出数周后归来的猎人，这种汤是庆功宴上的一种菜肴。如今这种汤被用于萨弗基亚各种场合的宴席。",en:"See-Food Pie a la Sufokia is a traditional dish thrown together out of whatever vaguely edible looking scraps the Sufokians could find to welcome home the fishermen who had been at sea for weeks hunting the Giant Kralove. Nowadays, they make it to celebrate all sorts of special occasions."};
descriptions["19110"]={cn:"有句著名的谚语说得好：\n\"逗你玩儿儿儿...\"",en:"As the well-known proverb says:\n\"The gift is a lie\""};
descriptions["19111"]={cn:"你最忠诚的伙伴！",en:"Your most loyal companion!"};
descriptions["19112"]={cn:"宠物染料可以于宠物设定介面中更改。此物品已无用处，可以将其分解掉。",en:"Pet colorings can be changed in the pet settings interface. This item is obsolete; you can recycle it."};
descriptions["19113"]={cn:"这个沙漏让你可以使用十二世界的时空裂痕",en:"This sandglass allows you to use the time rifts in the world."};
descriptions["19121"]={cn:"这个盾牌从四面八方保护你。",en:"This shield will protect you from attacks from the front, the back, and even from other dimensions."};
descriptions["19122"]={cn:"实用的匕首，可以用来刺伤另一个次元的人...或者更简单，从背后袭击。",en:"A useful dagger for sticking it to someone from another dimension... Or simply stabbing them in the back."};
descriptions["19123"]={cn:"所有械勒信徒都戴着的普通帽子。可能用来遮掩他们的假耳朵。",en:"An ordinary hat worn by all Xelor disciples. Probably to hide their fake ears."};
descriptions["19124"]={cn:"\"暂时\"共享给兄弟们一起用。",en:"A pair of epaulettes \"temporally\" shared between all the members of a brotherhood."};
descriptions["19125"]={cn:"传承靴子让我们想起械勒时装。",en:"Traditional Shoes to remind us of Xelor customs."};
descriptions["19126"]={cn:"在械勒信徒中炙手可热。",en:"This classic hand-holder is a favourite amongst Xelor disciples."};
descriptions["19127"]={cn:"献给未来开拓者。",en:"A breastplate for anyone who is abreast of future developments."};
descriptions["19128"]={cn:"永远站在时尚的前沿。",en:"In perpetual evolution, this cloak will always be in fashion."};
descriptions["19129"]={cn:"如果你能无限重复做一件事情，时光的意义何在。",en:"Who cares about eternity when you can do the same thing over and over again."};
descriptions["19130"]={cn:"非常有效，可惜不太持久。",en:"More effective than ever, unfortunately this hand won\'t last forever."};
descriptions["19131"]={cn:"你以为你在转圈，其实你眼花了。",en:"You might think you\'re going round in circles, but really you\'re staring into the void."};
descriptions["19132"]={cn:"根据你的需求给予诅咒或者祝福。",en:"Depending on who you ask, this weapon is either a curse or a godsend."};
descriptions["19133"]={cn:"虽然能穿过时光，但不一定每次都能击中你的敌人。",en:"This arrow, that invariably cuts through the air in the same direction, is not always the most practical tool for reaching your opponents."};
descriptions["19134"]={cn:"这个护肩非常小，这才是它厉害的地方。",en:"The real strength of these epaulettes lies in their delicacy."};
descriptions["19135"]={cn:"切断时间，空间以及敌人的脸，战斗中非常有用的剑。",en:"Cutting through time and space, and its opponents\' faces, this Sword is one of the most effective weapons in combat."};
descriptions["19136"]={cn:"随时准备接受新的挑战，每个时代都会有新的造型。",en:"Always ready for change, these Innovative Boots renew themselves once an eon. Well, almost."};
descriptions["19137"]={cn:"忠于原味，敢于创新。",en:"Be original, try something new, contradiction never hurt anyone."};
descriptions["19138"]={cn:"械勒神域西部，局部地区有大风，请系紧披风。",en:"Today, we will be experiencing strong winds along the western coast of the Xelorium, so don\'t forget to make sure your cloak\'s securely fastened!"};
descriptions["19139"]={cn:"比手表什么的实用多了，这根腰带能看时间，而且精确到秒。",en:"More practical than a watch or a pocket watch, this belt will let you know what time it is and is accurate to the second."};
descriptions["19140"]={cn:"随时准备进入战斗。",en:"Always alert, on fire, ready to let rip."};
descriptions["19141"]={cn:"准备出发，地图在手，天下我有。好吧，是他们说的。",en:"Set off on an adventure, map in hand, and you will find wonders. Well, that\'s what they told you anyway!"};
descriptions["19142"]={cn:"喝一杯来回忆一下美好的过去。干杯！",en:"There\'s nothing like reminiscing about the good old days over a drink. Cheers!"};
descriptions["19143"]={cn:"舒适耐用造型好，谁用谁知道。",en:"This shield offers durable protection and a more natural feel during combat."};
descriptions["19144"]={cn:"一把自我救赎的新纪元匕首。",en:"A dagger to seal the self-proclamation of the New Ancients."};
descriptions["19145"]={cn:"还不够赶紧下跪！",en:"Bow down before the Eternal!"};
descriptions["19146"]={cn:"这根指针古往今来一直受到人们的喜爱。有些人甚至在做这个任务的时候就已经疯了。",en:"This hand is respected throughout the ages. Some have even gone mad in their quest to get their hands on it."};
descriptions["19147"]={cn:"摸一下吓死你。没人想知道你是怎么摸到它的。",en:"This feather shocks you when you touch it. We don\'t want to know how you got your hands on it!"};
descriptions["19148"]={cn:"点击两下来把整组古代资源转换成新的符文粉末。古代资源需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["19149"]={cn:"前往地下城门口的兑奖机处兑换酷炫的奖励。",en:"Use the machine across from the dungeon to exchange your tokens for fantastic rewards."};
descriptions["19150"]={cn:"用于轻机械，使你的发明更加轻巧。",en:"Used in some of the softer mechanisms, the Meshed Feather adds a lighter touch to your creations."};
descriptions["19151"]={cn:"最基本机械都少不了日晷指针。",en:"A Dial Hand is necessary to make even the most basic mechanisms."};
descriptions["19152"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["19153"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["19154"]={cn:"值得你带回家的美味。",en:"A hearty dinner takes you back."};
descriptions["19155"]={cn:"比起在战斗后喝，在战斗前喝更好。",en:"This potion is best drunk before dangerous combats, not after them."};
descriptions["19156"]={cn:"马上帮你恢复体力，快到想不到。",en:"This bread can regenerate you faster than you can say loaf."};
descriptions["19157"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few drops should suffice."};
descriptions["19158"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few drops should suffice."};
descriptions["19159"]={cn:"这种美味是由亲爱的曾曾曾..曾祖母为你做的。好吧，也许没那么美味...",en:"This delicious gruel was made with love by your great, great.... great, great grandma. Ok, maybe she wasn\'t that good."};
descriptions["19160"]={cn:"马上帮你恢复体力，快到想不到。",en:"This bread can regenerate you faster than you can say loaf."};
descriptions["19161"]={cn:"后劲很大，喝完就算输了也不知道，真的。",en:"More strong than effective, this liquor will put enough wind in your sails for you to come out victorious even in defeat. Especially in defeat, actually."};
descriptions["19162"]={cn:"收集100块碎片，合成往昔指针。",en:"Collect 100 of these fragments to create a Bygone Hand."};
descriptions["19163"]={cn:"收集100块碎片，合成好运披风。",en:"Collect 100 of these fragments to create a Lucloak."};
descriptions["19164"]={cn:"使用这张卷轴，你将会回到角色选择界面，你可以在那儿选择新职业、性别和外观。此外，你还可以重新分配能力和天赋点数。注意，转职是永久的。",en:"Upon using this scroll, it is consumed, and you will return to the hero selection interface where you can choose your new class, sex, colors and clothes. Then, you can redistribute your abilities, spells and specialties. WARNING, THE CHANGE IS PERMANENT."};
descriptions["19165"]={cn:"使用这张卷轴，你将会回到角色选择界面，你可以在那儿选择新职业、性别和外观。此外，你还可以重新分配能力和天赋点数。注意，转职是永久的。",en:"Upon using this scroll, it is consumed, and you will return to the hero selection interface where you can choose your new class, sex, colors and clothes. Then, you can redistribute your abilities, spells and specialties. WARNING, THE CHANGE IS PERMANENT."};
descriptions["19166"]={cn:"使用这张卷轴，你将会回到角色选择界面，你可以在那儿选择新职业、性别和外观。此外，你还可以重新分配能力和天赋点数。注意，转职是永久的。",en:"Upon using this scroll, it is consumed, and you will be returned to the hero selection interface to choose your new class, sex, colors and clothes. Then, you can redistribute your abilities, spells and specialties. WARNING: THE CHANGE IS PERMANENT."};
descriptions["19167"]={cn:"斯蒂芬·西格尔开始战斗时总是用这玩意儿。也许这就是为什么人们认为他是个木头脑袋的原因。",en:"Stephen Seagull always used this stuff when staging fights. Perhaps that\'s why people accuse him of being so wooden."};
descriptions["19168"]={cn:"这种木材在许多方面都很特别。它会让你完全干涸。",en:"This wood is exceptional in many ways. It\'ll leave you completely dried out."};
descriptions["19169"]={cn:"这棵树枝的梦想是成为室内盆景。",en:"This cutting could be whatever it wants to be, but its dream is to be the inspiration for an air freshening spray."};
descriptions["19170"]={cn:"妥善地埋好这些种子，你会收获一颗漂亮的火山花。",en:"Plant these seeds correctly and you\'ll have a beautiful Volcanic Plant to look after."};
descriptions["19171"]={cn:"风干后，花瓣可以用来制造催人打喷嚏的粉末，用于头痛十分有效。",en:"Once dried, its flowers can be used to create a sneezing powder which is very effective against headaches."};
descriptions["19172"]={cn:"颜色黑暗，气味难闻，久久不散。",en:"This flower\'s darkish color is accompanied by a heavy, lingering smell."};
descriptions["19173"]={cn:"小小的种子居然能长出壮实的草莓株，结满了可口的果实。",en:"It\'s hard to believe that this tiny seed will give life to a robust strawberry plant, laden with delicious fruit."};
descriptions["19174"]={cn:"又大又甜又多汁的草莓；它的颜色和形状会让每个人的脸上都绽放笑容。",en:"Big, sweet, juicy strawberry; its color and shape will put a smile on everyone\'s face."};
descriptions["19175"]={cn:"这些草莓之所以是传奇，是因为找到它们比摘下来更难。最困难的事情是设法不在回家前吃掉它们。",en:"These strawberries are legendary because they are very difficult to find, then to pick. The most difficult thing is managing to get home without eating them."};
descriptions["19176"]={cn:"斑铁块是普通铁块氧化后带上了一些卡玛斑点的铁块。也许看上去不炫酷，但是一样价值不菲。",en:"Acid Sryanure is extremely corrosive and is used to rapidly oxidize a metal in order to give it that charming old feel."};
descriptions["19177"]={cn:"锈铁矿在埃努卓神域真是不堪入目，因此不反对甚至鼓励人们去采集。",en:"Sryanure Mineral must be carefully extracted so as not to release any poison."};
descriptions["19178"]={cn:"这是海洋，这是老板鱼。这种鱼的行为非常奇怪，没有人知道它是比骑士更笨，还是一种智力超群的生物。",en:"There\'s the ocean and there is the Vandame. This fish behaves so strangely that no one knows whether it\'s stupider than a Iop, or a life form of superior intelligence."};
descriptions["19179"]={cn:"这是一条聪明的鱼。",en:"This is a smart fish."};
descriptions["19180"]={cn:"这老东西看上去已经没用了。",en:"This old thing doesn\'t seem very useful anymore."};
descriptions["19181"]={cn:"忍耐是美德，使其魅力无穷。",en:"His virtues endure and his charm has been unequalled since forever."};
descriptions["19182"]={cn:"点击两下来把整组古代资源转换成新的资源。古代资源需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["19183"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["19184"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["19185"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["19186"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
