descriptions["19188"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["19189"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["19190"]={cn:"前往地下城门口的兑奖机处兑换酷炫的奖励。",en:"Use the machine across from the dungeon to exchange your tokens for fantastic rewards."};
descriptions["19191"]={cn:"前往地下城门口的兑奖机处兑换酷炫的奖励。",en:"Use the machine across from the dungeon to exchange your tokens for fantastic rewards."};
descriptions["19192"]={cn:"收集100块碎片，合成好运披风。（帐号绑定）",en:"Collect 100 of these fragments to create a pair of Lucloak (linked to the account)."};
descriptions["19193"]={cn:"收集100块碎片，合成往昔指针（帐号绑定）。",en:"Collect 100 of these fragments to create a Bygone Hand (linked to the account)."};
descriptions["19194"]={cn:"这件披风可遇而不可求，不过既然你已经穿上了说明也不是那么难以获得。",en:"This cloak may be the physical manifestation of luck itself, but the fact that you\'re wearing it wasn\'t left to chance."};
descriptions["19195"]={cn:"这根指针古往今来一直受到人们的喜爱。有些人甚至在做这个任务的时候就已经疯了。",en:"This hand is respected throughout the ages. Some have even gone mad in their quest to get their hands on it."};
descriptions["19196"]={cn:"晶晶凉，透心凉！",en:"You can sweat off the pods, or just freeze off entire extremities!"};
descriptions["19200"]={cn:"一个使你获得\"镜旅人\"称号的卷轴。",en:"A scroll which allows you to obtain the \"Mirror Voyager\" title."};
descriptions["19201"]={cn:"挥舞一把普通的剑不如挥舞一把带着火的剑！",en:"Brandishing a sword is good. Brandishing a flaming sword is better. Clearly."};
descriptions["19203"]={cn:"美丽记忆，永久珍藏。",en:"A nice trophy for your personal collection."};
descriptions["19204"]={cn:"美丽记忆，永久珍藏。",en:"A nice trophy for your personal collection."};
descriptions["19205"]={cn:"美丽记忆，永久珍藏。",en:"A nice trophy for your personal collection."};
descriptions["19207"]={cn:"宠物装备可以于宠物设定介面中更改。此物品已无用处，可以将其分解掉。",en:"Pet equipment can be changed in the pet settings interface. This item is obsolete; you can recycle it."};
descriptions["19210"]={cn:"独特的徽章，戴起来之后化身异度旅者。",en:"This emblem will strengthen your Eliotrope slightly."};
descriptions["19212"]={cn:"使你可以破解系统，激活最后一个次元传送门。",en:"Allows you to deactivate the security system and activate the the last dimensional portal before the temple."};
descriptions["19213"]={cn:"既有智慧，又有良好的信誉。这件外套使你在任何情况下都能安然无恙应对的全部局面。",en:"Good standing as well as wisdom. This coat is all the kit you need to conquer without peril in all situations."};
descriptions["19214"]={cn:"你的后背会一尘不染。正如一位智者所说，“往事可鉴不可追”。",en:"Your back will be spotless. And, as a wise man once said, \"the past is a place of reference, not a place of residence\"."};
descriptions["19215"]={cn:"这件披风会让你周围的人想要团结起来。",en:"This cape will make those around you want to close ranks."};
descriptions["19216"]={cn:"这件庄严的斗篷象征着你文化的丰裕、尊严和社会地位。",en:"This stately cloak represents the richness of your culture, your dignity, and your social status."};
descriptions["19217"]={cn:"戴在脖子上的玛瑙是搭配任何服装的绝佳方式。",en:"Onyx worn around your neck is a great way of accessorizing any outfit."};
descriptions["19218"]={cn:"你的华丽装束也许会给你某种风格，但没有人会误认为你是个挥金如土的人，而不是一个穷战士。",en:"Your fine attire might give you certain style, but nobody\'s going to mistake you for a big spender rather than a poor fighter."};
descriptions["19220"]={cn:"去探险再也不会像以前一样了。这双靴子不会破洞、防水、鞋底永不磨损。",en:"Going on an expedition will never be the same again. These boots are hole-proof, waterproof, and the sole never wears down."};
descriptions["19221"]={cn:"不要害怕继续前进。你的脚步将永远引领你走向未来。",en:"Don\'t be afraid to move on. Your steps will always lead you toward the future."};
descriptions["19222"]={cn:"这是毫无疑问的。你真的是阴影王子。",en:"There\'s no doubt about it. You really are the prince of shadows."};
descriptions["19223"]={cn:"这双纯金制成的靴子会把你的敌人远远甩在身后。不要穿太久，否则你的脚会起水泡的！",en:"These boots made from solid gold will leave your enemies in the dust. Don\'t wear them too long, or you might get blisters!"};
descriptions["19225"]={cn:"它的颜色让你想起了美丽的夏日，而你在等待，希望有一天，他们会回来。",en:"Its color reminds you of beautiful summer days, while you wait in the hope that, one day, they\'ll return."};
descriptions["19226"]={cn:"一个能击退邪恶势力并照亮地平线的戒指。",en:"A ring that repels the forces of evil and lights up the horizon."};
descriptions["19227"]={cn:"在你拿到手之前，很少有工匠知道这件艺术品的存在。但现在是时候给予它应有的认可了。",en:"Very few craftsmen knew of the existence of this work of art before you got your hands on it. But now it\'s time to give it the recognition it deserves."};
descriptions["19228"]={cn:"很少有头盔能同时兼顾力量和精美。这个会让你看起来像个王子，但是外表是有欺骗性的...",en:"Not many helms successfully combine both power and refinement. This one will make you look like a prince, but looks can be deceiving..."};
descriptions["19231"]={cn:"任何一个老兵都会很乐意听从戴着这种头盔的人的命令，不管他们在哪个战场上。",en:"Any veteran will be happy to follow the orders of the person wearing this headgear, regardless of which battlefield they\'re on."};
descriptions["19232"]={cn:"它帮助你超越你身体的限制。这也是节省空间的好方法，因为你终于可以用一些更有用的东西来取代你的大脑，比如鸟窝或者跳踢踏舞的食人族。",en:"It helps you see beyond the physical limitations of your body. It\'s also a great space-saver, because you can finally replace your brain with something more useful, like a bird\'s nest or a tap-dancing Kanniball."};
descriptions["19233"]={cn:"你总是在后半夜戴上这个头盔。没关系，因为你内心的阴影在你的世界观上映射出了永远的阴影。",en:"It\'s always midnight when you\'re wearing this helmet. Not that it matters, since the shadows in your heart cast a permanent dark hue over the way you see the world."};
descriptions["19234"]={cn:"这是某个人戴的头盔的不完全复制品。简而言之，由于头盔的历史记录不够精确，我们无法知道它最初的样子。",en:"This helmet is an inexact replica of the one worn by a certain individual. In short, given the lack of precision surrounding the helmet\'s history, there\'s no way of knowing what it originally looked like."};
descriptions["19236"]={cn:"这条腰带系在腰间可以让你看起来更苗条...我是说从前面。",en:"This belt is worn around the waist to make you look slimmer... from the front."};
descriptions["19237"]={cn:"它把所有的东西都放在合适的位置。",en:"It holds everything in place."};
descriptions["19238"]={cn:"Bakfu 是一个军事政府，位于萨弗基亚的一个小岛上，由一个曾经拥有这个护身符的 Gunsho 领导。",en:"The Bakfu was a military government on a small mountainous island of Sufokia, led by a Gunsho who used to own this amulet."};
descriptions["19239"]={cn:"戴上这个护身符会让你比以往任何时候都更有灵性。",en:"Wearing this amulet will make you more spiritual than ever."};
descriptions["19240"]={cn:"从玛瑙塔的黑暗熔炉里制作出来。",en:"It was set in the Black Forge of the Onyx Tower."};
descriptions["19241"]={cn:"传说这个金色的护身符曾被一只金色的龙所佩戴。它是无价之宝，有着庄严的美丽和力量。",en:"Legend has it this golden amulet was once worn by a golden dragon. It\'s a priceless jewel, with majestic beauty and power."};
descriptions["19242"]={cn:"用水晶球装饰的美丽的时钟指针，它从水晶球中汲取力量。",en:"A beautiful clock hand embellished with a crystalline orb, from which it draws its power."};
descriptions["19243"]={cn:"一种可以像手套一样轻易地扇某人耳光以激怒他们的棍子。",en:"A staff that you can slap someone with as easily as gloves in order to provoke them."};
descriptions["19244"]={cn:"这个盾牌很容易受到攻击，所以要在你面前稳稳地拿住它。",en:"This shield is really quite happy taking hits, so hold it solidly before you."};
descriptions["19246"]={cn:"这些地图将确保没有人听到你的窃窃私语“恶作剧完毕！”",en:"These maps will ensure that no one ever hears you whisper \"mischief managed!\""};
descriptions["19247"]={cn:"这把匕首一旦刺进失败者身上，就能决定谁是胜利者。",en:"This dagger determines who is the winner once stuck into the loser."};
descriptions["19248"]={cn:"手中有了这把剑，你在对战友演讲时会使自己受到鼓舞。",en:"With this sword in your hands, you\'ll be inspired during your speeches to your companions in arms."};
descriptions["19249"]={cn:"这把剑什么都不怕，谁也不怕；它是如此无所畏惧，以至于你对任何事情都毫不在乎。",en:"This sword fears nothing and no one; it is so fearless that you too won\'t give a tuppence about anything."};
descriptions["19251"]={cn:"有了这个，你就能把那些自称是赢家的人赶下颁奖台。",en:"Armed with this, you\'ll be able to knock all those self-proclaimed winners off their podiums."};
descriptions["19252"]={cn:"这把铲子能以极快的速度挖出敌人的坟墓。",en:"This shovel will dig your enemies\' tombs at breakneck speed."};
descriptions["19253"]={cn:"献给创生之力的信徒。",en:"For those who believe in the power of Wakfu."};
descriptions["19254"]={cn:"新鲜，Q弹，塔挞！",en:"Surprisingly good between the teeth!"};
descriptions["19255"]={cn:"外焦里嫩，味道鲜美，你我共享。",en:"Golden brown and delicious, these meatballs are for sharing."};
descriptions["19257"]={cn:"你在做出一番痛苦的抉择之后，终于得到了这个助手，同时他也是斯拉姆神域之旅的幸存者之一。",en:"After making an agonizing choice, you have acquired the services of the sidekick who also survived the episode with Sram."};
descriptions["19258"]={cn:"你在做出一番痛苦的抉择之后，终于得到了这个助手，同时他也是斯拉姆神域之旅的幸存者之一。",en:"After making an agonizing choice, you have acquired the services of the sidekick who also survived the episode with Sram."};
descriptions["19259"]={cn:"你可以将助手绑定至你的帐号并在战斗中使用。注意！除去个别特殊情况，这项操作无法被取消。",en:"This item enables you to link this sidekick to your account and use it in combat. Careful! This action cannot be undone, except under certain circumstances."};
descriptions["19261"]={cn:"你可以将助手绑定至你的账号并在战斗中使用。注意！除去个别特殊情况，这项操作无法被取消。",en:"This item enables you to link this sidekick to your account and use it in combat. Careful! This action cannot be undone, except under certain circumstances."};
descriptions["19262"]={cn:"你可以将助手绑定至你的账号并在战斗中使用。注意！除去个别特殊情况，这项操作无法被取消。",en:"This item enables you to link this sidekick to your account and use it in combat. Careful! This action cannot be undone, except under certain circumstances."};
descriptions["19265"]={cn:"正义炫酷！",en:"Justice is a dish best served cool!"};
descriptions["19266"]={cn:"跟着你到处走的小乌鸦！",en:"A little Crobak to follow you wherever you go!"};
descriptions["19273"]={cn:"可以装备于战斗绵球，让他们和熔岩绵球长得一模一样。",en:"A Gobball War Chief skin to make you look like a Gobbalrog."};
descriptions["19274"]={cn:"战斗型绵球首领，用来和一群敌人战斗。",en:"A Gobball War Chief trained to fight groups of enemies."};
descriptions["19275"]={cn:"战斗型绵球首领，用来和敌人远距离作战。",en:"A Gobball War Chief trained to fight from a distance."};
descriptions["19276"]={cn:"战斗型绵球首领，用来和敌人近距离作战。",en:"A gobball war chief specialized in the art of melee fighting."};
descriptions["19277"]={cn:"战斗型绵球首领，用来和敌人一对一作战。",en:"A Gobball War Chief trained to fight against a single enemy."};
descriptions["19278"]={cn:"这本书是由械勒亲手给你的。书页上的字仿佛在震动着，想要告诉你字里行间的与众不同。每一个句子都是由不同的人在不同的时间写下的。",en:"This book was given to you by Xelor himself. The text on the pages seems to vibrate, as if wanting to form different words. Each sentence seems to have been written by a different person at a different point in time."};
descriptions["19279"]={cn:"老板，来两斤胡萝卜汁呗！",en:"Thankfully, Cawwots awe still pwesent in the Wowld of Twelve. You wouldn\'t have it any othew way."};
descriptions["19280"]={cn:"最炫雷蛇风！",en:"Play the game... with style!"};
descriptions["19281"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few drops should suffice."};
descriptions["19290"]={cn:"这是一个巧克力书架！可别吃掉了，它只是一个书架。",en:"A chocolate bookshelf! But don\'t eat it. It\'s still a bookshelf."};
descriptions["19292"]={cn:"幻魔可以把一件物品变成另一件同类型、同等级或低等级物品的模样。\n请注意，使用幻魔后提供外观的物品将消失。",en:"The Mimisymbic lets you give an item the appearance of another item that\'s the same type.\nBe careful: the item whose appearance is transferred is destroyed during fusion."};
descriptions["19297"]={cn:"给你一个地道的复活节主题庇护袋！艾诺普已经牺牲得够多了，好好对待它。",en:"With this kit, you can have a 100% Fleaster-themed Haven Bag! Etnop made a huge sacrifice for you - take care of it."};
descriptions["19298"]={cn:"将你变成一只可爱的小兔兔。",en:"This potion will turn you into a cute little Wodent."};
descriptions["19309"]={cn:"你想想里面可能有什么？",en:"But what could be inside this basket that Etnop has given you?"};
descriptions["19310"]={cn:"这个特殊的篮子里面有什么呢？",en:"But what does this special basket have inside?"};
descriptions["19311"]={cn:"科尔巴岛上非常珍贵的商品。",en:"Various merchandise to deliver in Kelba"};
descriptions["19313"]={cn:"恢复最大生命的10%。",en:"Full of chocolate! (and calories)"};
descriptions["19315"]={cn:"用于和鸦人做交易。",en:"Merchandise to trade with the Raskaws"};
descriptions["19316"]={cn:"用于和鸦人做交易。",en:"Merchandise to trade with the Raskaws"};
descriptions["19317"]={cn:"用于和鸦人做交易。",en:"Merchandise to trade with the Raskaws"};
descriptions["19318"]={cn:"有个怪物让艾诺普将它的彩蛋变成白巧克力做的装备，于是就有了这种头盔。",en:"A monster who wanted to make Etnop sad transformed his precious eggs into armor made of white chocolate, and this is the helmet."};
descriptions["19319"]={cn:"有个怪物让艾诺普将它的彩蛋变成黑巧克力做的装备，于是就有了这种头盔。",en:"A monster who wanted to make Etnop sad transformed his precious eggs into armor made of dark chocolate, and this is the helmet."};
descriptions["19320"]={cn:"有个怪物让艾诺普将它的彩蛋变成白巧克力做的装备，於是就有了这种胸甲。",en:"A monster who wanted to make Etnop sad transformed his precious eggs into armor made of white chocolate, and this is the breastplate."};
descriptions["19321"]={cn:"有个怪物让艾诺普将它的彩蛋变成黑巧克力做的装备，於是就有了这种胸甲。",en:"A monster who wanted to make Etnop sad transformed his precious eggs into armor made of dark chocolate, and this is the breastplate."};
descriptions["19322"]={cn:"有个怪物让艾诺普将它的彩蛋变成白巧克力做的装备，于是就有了这种靴子。",en:"A monster who wanted to make Etnop sad transformed his precious eggs into armor made of white chocolate, and these are the epaulettes."};
descriptions["19323"]={cn:"有个怪物让艾诺普将它的彩蛋变成黑巧克力做的装备，于是就有了这种靴子。",en:"A monster who wanted to make Etnop sad transformed his precious eggs into armor made of dark chocolate, and these are the epaulettes."};
descriptions["19324"]={cn:"有个怪物让艾诺普将它的彩蛋变成白巧克力做的装备，于是就有了这种斗篷。",en:"A monster who wanted to make Etnop sad transformed his precious eggs into armor made of white chocolate, and this is the cape."};
descriptions["19325"]={cn:"有个怪物让艾诺普将它的彩蛋变成黑巧克力做的装备，于是就有了这种斗篷。",en:"A monster who wanted to make Etnop sad transformed his precious eggs into armor made of dark chocolate, and this is the cape."};
descriptions["19326"]={cn:"有个怪物让艾诺普将它的彩蛋变成白巧克力做的装备，于是就有了这种靴子。",en:"A monster who wanted to make Etnop sad transformed his precious eggs into armor made of white chocolate, and these are the boots."};
descriptions["19327"]={cn:"有个怪物让艾诺普将它的彩蛋变成黑巧克力做的装备，于是就有了这种靴子。",en:"A monster who wanted to make Etnop sad transformed his precious eggs into armor made of dark chocolate, and these are the boots."};
descriptions["19328"]={cn:"你梦想成为乌鸦吗？",en:"Have you never dreamed of being a crow?"};
descriptions["19335"]={cn:"连结至酋长之魂的美丽羽毛，或者至少是个高级赝品。",en:"Magnificent wings linked to the Orrok spirit. Or at least a very good imitation!"};
descriptions["19336"]={cn:"这个胸甲用家禽身上的材料制成的。",en:"These Epaulettes are made with all the things a fowl dreams of wearing daily."};
descriptions["19337"]={cn:"大酋长庇佑的护甲。应该会保护你不受伤害，至少不用担心来自正面的攻击。",en:"This shield was blessed by the original Grand Orrok. It should guarantee you\'re well protected - at least from a frontal assault."};
descriptions["19338"]={cn:"在山上你必须穿鞋子，这会让你保住小命！",en:"In the mountains, you have to keep on your feet - it will help keep you from falling to your death!"};
descriptions["19339"]={cn:"和祖先之间的羁绊让他们变得更加强大。",en:"The link the Raskaw people have with their ancestors makes all the more powerful."};
descriptions["19340"]={cn:"这是一位村庄长老穿戴的头饰，证明他不是普通的村民。",en:"This headgear is worn by the village chief in order to distinguish himself from his peers."};
descriptions["19341"]={cn:"一根包含对祖先敬畏之情的羽毛。",en:"Plumage that evokes respect for ancestors and local customs."};
descriptions["19342"]={cn:"可以称之为十二世界最完美的护符，现在仍然在你的手上。",en:"This Amulet has passed through all the most beautiful markets in the World of Twelve. And yet, it still ended up in your grubby hands. Imagine that."};
descriptions["19343"]={cn:"有了这块缠布，你已经是最森林中最酷炫的了。",en:"With this loincloth, you can have the best-looking assets in the woods."};
descriptions["19344"]={cn:"象征你是科尔巴山中的一员。",en:"A symbol that shows you are a member of the people of the Kelba mountains."};
descriptions["19345"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["19346"]={cn:"鸦人最令人不寒而栗的庇护。",en:"One of the most sacred blessings that the Raskaw people can bestow on a young recruit."};
descriptions["19347"]={cn:"年轻的流氓鸦到了一定的年纪后就会用它们的翅膀飞走并在科尔巴岛上建立起自己的巢穴。",en:"As soon as young Raskaws reach the age of adventure, they use their wings to fly away and establish their very own encampment in the Lands of Kelba."};
descriptions["19348"]={cn:"你看上去就像克罗伯当地人一样。",en:"You look like you came straight out of the Kreublo."};
descriptions["19349"]={cn:"别想着自己也能像鸟那样在天上飞...后果可不只是掉几根毛而已...",en:"Don\'t bother trying a flying raid like you\'ve seen the birds do - you risk leaving more than just a few feathers behind..."};
descriptions["19350"]={cn:"穿上以后能让你回避一些普通的反击。",en:"These shoulderguards let you dodge regular counterattacks when attacking merchant convoys."};
descriptions["19351"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["19352"]={cn:"克罗伯年轻人通常拥有更加松软的羽毛。当然其实差别并不明显。",en:"Kreublo youths generally have softer and silkier plumage than the adults. The difference is really pretty subtle though."};
descriptions["19353"]={cn:"这个护符给予克罗伯村年轻人酋长般的勇气，让他们能穿过科尔巴岛。",en:"This Amulet is offered to young members of Kreublos winging their way through the Lands of Kelba to give them the courage of the Orrok."};
descriptions["19354"]={cn:"令人垂涎的绷带，用来抚慰冒险者充满鲜血的手。",en:"A very sought after bandage, for soothing the murderous hands of young raiders."};
descriptions["19355"]={cn:"克罗伯村的年轻人最喜欢的饰物，这腰带让他们的羽毛显得很漂亮。",en:"The Krawsh embellishes the outfits of Kreublo youths, and really shows off their plumage too."};
descriptions["19356"]={cn:"简单好用，你可以钩敌人，也可以收割小麦。",en:"Very handy while raiding convoys - you can mow down the enemy while mowing down wheat."};
descriptions["19357"]={cn:"生成于世间万物，可以轻易的划过克罗伯的羽毛。",en:"This dagger is made of anything and everything, and can easily slip between the feathers of an intrepid Krueblo youth."};
descriptions["19358"]={cn:"鸦人传说尖酸长枪是大酋长带过来的。在月圆之时它会与你的灵魂立下契约。",en:"The Raskaw legend says that this lance was brought to the Lands of Kelba by the original Grand Orrok. It will reinforce your link to the sacred spirit on contact, on nights where the full moon is partly hidden by clouds."};
descriptions["19359"]={cn:"能让机械鸦免去风吹雨打之苦。",en:"Once ripped off, the head of the Korbot makes a pretty good head covering for windy, rainy days."};
descriptions["19360"]={cn:"非常沉重的腰带，只能在特殊场合佩戴。当然，你能拥有已经很不容易了。",en:"This very heavy belt is usually only worn on special occasions, but then again, having one in your inventory is a special occasion."};
descriptions["19361"]={cn:"可以戴在任何鸦人上。",en:"The bits and pieces can be used by any Kraw."};
descriptions["19362"]={cn:"这是卡波克的第一批样品。",en:"These boots were part of Kabrok\'s first prototypes."};
descriptions["19363"]={cn:"这是卡波克的第一批样品。",en:"This cape was part of Kabrok\'s first prototypes."};
descriptions["19364"]={cn:"这是卡波克的第一批样品。",en:"This breastplate was part of Kabrok\'s first prototypes."};
descriptions["19365"]={cn:"这是卡波克的第一批样品。",en:"This ring was part of Kabrok\'s first prototypes."};
descriptions["19366"]={cn:"曾将在科尔巴商店热卖，现在由于非常稀少变得非常有收藏价值。只有卡波克和一些收藏家还拥有几件。",en:"Once sold in the Kelba shops, it\'s now only available at Kabrok\'s and from the occasional collector."};
descriptions["19367"]={cn:"为了让护肩看上去有质感，所以采用金属作为制作材料。",en:"These epaulettes are made of a metal that was worked extensively in order to give it that rusted copper look."};
descriptions["19368"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["19369"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["19370"]={cn:"这种特殊的奖章让你能在你的国家换取坐骑的国家装饰。",en:"This special token lets you get a harness in your nation\'s colors to equip your petsmount."};
descriptions["19374"]={cn:"纯手工打造，能更有效的治疗伤口。",en:"This bandage is more solid than the makeshift one and considerably reduces the appearance of scar tissue for severe wounds."};
descriptions["19375"]={cn:"前往地下城门口的兑奖机处兑换酷炫的奖励。",en:"Use the machine across from the dungeon to exchange your tokens for fantastic rewards."};
descriptions["19376"]={cn:"点击两下来把整组古代资源转换成新的资源。古代资源需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["19377"]={cn:"拉动骨头是鸦人们的一种习俗。酋长小骨是不错的选择。",en:"Drawing bones is a bit of a passion among the Raskaw people. Drawing an Orrok\'s Ossicle is always considered a very good omen."};
descriptions["19378"]={cn:"一条支撑你裤子的美丽腰带。",en:"A beautifully befeathered belt for bracing your britches."};
descriptions["19379"]={cn:"是加了特技的。",en:"Never stop Kring."};
descriptions["19380"]={cn:"没有比这种流线型的衣服更适合打斗了。",en:"For scrapping, nothing\'s better than a light breastplate that lets you move fluidly."};
descriptions["19381"]={cn:"鸦人留下最后的护符。",en:"An amulet which is all the rage among the Raskaws."};
descriptions["19382"]={cn:"适用于一场说走就走的旅行。",en:"Great for air races - not so great for walking."};
descriptions["19383"]={cn:"流氓鸦经常使用的武器。摩擦摩擦！",en:"The longsword of Raskaw guards. A teariffic sword!"};
descriptions["19385"]={cn:"滑不滑你滑不滑我滑不滑你滑...",en:"How many snaps would a Snapper snap if..."};
descriptions["19386"]={cn:"从外表上来看，或者从声音上来听，你就是一个天赋异禀失聪作曲家。",en:"From the looks of it, or rather, the sound, it seems you\'re a gifted deaf composer."};
descriptions["19387"]={cn:"我自己其实就是一个宝物，我的钥匙在谁手上？",en:"At the heart of your being lies a treasure - but who holds the key?"};
descriptions["19388"]={cn:"你精通那些大家都不知道的文字。",en:"You are the master of unspoken words."};
descriptions["19391"]={cn:"水节上最好的装扮！",en:"The perfect costume to celebrate the Water Festival!"};
descriptions["19392"]={cn:"穿上一身帅气的衣服去求婚吧！",en:"Propose and get shot down in only the most handsome garments!"};
descriptions["19393"]={cn:"加入女武神行列吧！很威猛的！",en:"Join the Valkyrie army! You\'ve got the look!"};
descriptions["19394"]={cn:"梦想成真了？真不敢相信！\n你毫无疑问是巡回武场的最强者，所以你有理由相信！",en:"You\'re not exactly a dream come true,\nbut you\'re the best of the Mobile Arenas, so you\'ll have to do!"};
descriptions["19395"]={cn:"多亏了这件装束，你再也不用为领导一堆狂热的蒙面人而烦恼了。",en:"Thanks to this great hat, you won\'t have any problem leading your ga... your guild of fervent Hoodlums."};
descriptions["19396"]={cn:"有什么？",en:"What item will you get in this mystery box?"};
descriptions["19397"]={cn:"有什么？",en:"What item will you get in this mystery box?"};
descriptions["19398"]={cn:"有什么？",en:"What item will you get in this mystery box?"};
descriptions["19399"]={cn:"有什么？",en:"What item will you get in this mystery box?"};
descriptions["19400"]={cn:"有什么？",en:"What item will you get in this mystery box?"};
descriptions["19401"]={cn:"有什么？",en:"What item will you get in this mystery box?"};
descriptions["19402"]={cn:"有什么？",en:"What item will you get in this mystery box?"};
descriptions["19403"]={cn:"有什么？",en:"What item will you get in this mystery box?"};
descriptions["19404"]={cn:"有什么？",en:"What item will you get in this mystery box?"};
descriptions["19405"]={cn:"在你的庇护袋里看上去很完美。",en:"This miniature will look perfect in your Haven Bag."};
descriptions["19406"]={cn:"你有没有做梦骑上黑鸦？虽然那不太可能发生，但这个军鸟装饰能让你身临其境。",en:"Haven\'t you ever dreamed of riding the Black Crow\'s mount? Since that\'s not likely to happen, this Dragoturkey harness will let you pretend."};
descriptions["19408"]={cn:"前往地下城门口的兑奖机处兑换酷炫的奖励。",en:"Use the machine in the dungeon to exchange your tokens for fantastic rewards."};
descriptions["19409"]={cn:"在你的庇护袋里看上去很完美。",en:"This miniature will look perfect in your Haven Bag."};
descriptions["19410"]={cn:"所有冒险者梦寐以求的谜之护符，你值得拥有！",en:"This amulet is highly sought-after by all the high-level adventurers, and you\'ve got it. They\'ll be so jealous!"};
descriptions["19411"]={cn:"最珍贵的指环就应该戴在最好看的那根手指上，让周围的朋友羡慕无比！",en:"Be sure to wear this ring on whatever finger(s) you may use to perform your favorite hand gestures - those on the receiving end will surely appreciate it!"};
descriptions["19412"]={cn:"穿上之后能让您立足悬崖。",en:"Thanks to these boots, you\'ll even be able to go straight up a vertical cliff!"};
descriptions["19413"]={cn:"传说中最别致的斗篷之一，如果说被羽毛蹭得奇痒无比也叫别致的话。",en:"They say this cape is one of the most chic capes. They\'re obviously not taking into account the itchiness caused by the feathers..."};
descriptions["19414"]={cn:"世间稀有的梦幻装备，得到它你做梦也会笑。",en:"This fantastic helmet is likely one of the rarest that you\'ll ever obtain. You must be dreaming."};
descriptions["19415"]={cn:"再也不怕被小人戳腰啦。",en:"This will help to protect you from particularly vicious blows."};
descriptions["19416"]={cn:"肩膀上面有什么？不是脑袋就是肩甲！",en:"If you haven\'t got a good head on your shoulders, it\'s best to have good armor on them."};
descriptions["19417"]={cn:"抵挡猛烈攻击，给您加倍信心。",en:"This Breastplate can take even the roughest blows - that oughtta make you a bit more confident in the arena."};
descriptions["19418"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["19419"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["19420"]={cn:"亮出黑鸦徽章，证明你的力量战无不克。",en:"Displaying the Black Crow emblem proves your endurance in combat."};
descriptions["19421"]={cn:"亮出白鸦徽章，证明你会利用智慧取胜。",en:"Displaying the White Crow emblem shows that you\'re not limited to battling like a Iop."};
descriptions["19422"]={cn:"重铸这柄剑的人将成为人皇。",en:"Recovering the Steel Beak Sword is an accomplishment few adventurers have managed!"};
descriptions["19423"]={cn:"趁龙猪大人睡觉的时候偷来的宝贝。没了它，龙猪现在只能一肚子横肉露在外边。",en:"This belt was stolen from the Dragon Pig while he slept. Now his gut hangs pendulously, and he\'s furious!"};
descriptions["19424"]={cn:"被一伙土匪从软橡树处劫掠的戒指，不久却被另一伙人给抢走。",en:"After taking this ring from the Soft Oak, it seems that this group of Riktus came across someone stronger than them!"};
descriptions["19425"]={cn:"从吸血城堡中散落的宝贝，能够号令世上的雌性食尸鬼。",en:"Stolen from Vampyro\'s Castle, this ring will make all the Ghouls tremble! Pretty ghoul, eh?"};
descriptions["19426"]={cn:"据称只有土匪长老才有资格穿戴的斗篷，其实谁穿都一样。",en:"Only the most seasoned Riktus have the right to wear this cape. But that doesn\'t stop everyone from doing it."};
descriptions["19427"]={cn:"无主之地，狂怒之地！",en:"All the rage in the Wild Estate!"};
descriptions["19429"]={cn:"使用了最为奇特的材料，令老多啦旧貌换新颜。不过，如果说它很成功的话，似乎有点夸张。",en:"Using only the most dubious ingredients, you\'ve managed to give the old Dora a new look. However, to call it successful might be exaggerating."};
descriptions["19430"]={cn:"如此可爱的设计，连鸟儿都在你身边飞舞了。很棒吧？",en:"With a slightly more charming appearance, you\'ll have the birds all aflutter. Classy, no?"};
descriptions["19431"]={cn:"你在铁喙的战利品里发现这个东西，但你不太清楚它是干什么用的...",en:"You found this in Steel Beak\'s loot, but you\'re not quite sure what to do with it..."};
descriptions["19432"]={cn:"N.I.O.是一个每周日晚上都会在阿斯图布下水道开会的委员会。没有人知道每个字母代表什么，因为成员都是昆虫爱好者，喜欢把秘密藏在心中，可能代表着昆虫的零食，药品，亦或是更加恐怖的东西。",en:"The N.I.O. is a committee which meets every Sunday evening in the depths of the Astrub Sewers. No one knows what the acronym stands for, because the members of the committee, who were big insect lovers, took the secret to their graves after confusing their favorite treat, the Phix, with the fatal Bhug! It looks good on you though, and that\'s what matters."};
descriptions["19433"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["19434"]={cn:"除了让你急不可耐地想要跳上高处抓挠窗帘外，装备这件宝物能给您额外的八条生命。传说这是一件属于艾卡菲利神的上古神器。",en:"Aside from the irrepressible urge to jump everywhere and climb the drapes, wearing these paws will give you the distinct impression of having lived just over 8 lives. Could it be an ancient artifact of the god Ecaflip?"};
descriptions["19435"]={cn:"用辛苦获得的铁喙奖章来兑换装备吧。",en:"You can trade in this hard-won token for pieces of equipment."};
descriptions["19436"]={cn:"纪念你曾经把铁喙揍成羽绒被。",en:"A battle trophy to remind you of that one time when you made Steel Beak into an eiderdown."};
descriptions["19437"]={cn:"蓬松蓬松，一身轻松。",en:"The Steel Beak Feather will make sure you always have a bit of fluff!"};
descriptions["19440"]={cn:"如果你头脑过热，只需要把头放在孵化器下面，就会变得开心了。",en:"If you brain\'s overheating, you just need to slide your meninges under the incubator. Your neurons will be happy."};
descriptions["19441"]={cn:"第二批机械翼样品，还不够支撑起整个机械鸦的重量。",en:"The second prototype of the Korbot\'s mechanical wings. It wasn\'t strong enough to support the Korbot\'s overall weight."};
descriptions["19442"]={cn:"卡波克自制，第一批机械鸦肩甲样品。",en:"The first prototype of the Korbotaulettes, made by Kabrok himself."};
descriptions["19443"]={cn:"卡波克自制，第一批机械鸦靴子样品。",en:"The first prototype of the Kroboots, made by Kabrok himself."};
descriptions["19444"]={cn:"第一次改造机械鸦的样品。看样子失败了。",en:"A first attempt at modeling the torso of the Korbot. Apparently, it was a failure."};
descriptions["19445"]={cn:"抵御外部和内部伤害的1号防护，常用于机械鸦的防护措施中。",en:"Protection number 1 against all internal and external damage, used in the Korbot\'s protection."};
descriptions["19446"]={cn:"这是蝙蝠球的心脏在死去后结晶的样子。当然，商店是买不到的。",en:"The heart of a Borbat crystalized in this form after its death. The item is, however, completely unsalable in a shop."};
descriptions["19447"]={cn:"夹紧指环能很好的将两种圆柱形零件拼在一起。如果你需要连结这两种零件的话，应该会用上它。",en:"The Clamp Ring is good for maintaining a connection between two cylindrical pieces. So if you need to reattach something cylindrical, it might be useful."};
descriptions["19448"]={cn:"这是一个很破旧的切纸器，卡波克需要用它来打开很多信封。毋庸置疑，也是卡波克自制的。",en:"The point of this paper cutter is a bit worn. Kabrok must have opened a lot of letter. Without a doubt, instructions on building his Korbot."};
descriptions["19449"]={cn:"只是一个酒桶盖子。也许卡波克想用来装在机械鸦身上，但是也看不出来。哦对了，这还可以当作一个不错的护甲。",en:"Just a barrel lid. Maybe Kabrok expected to use it as a part of his Korbot, but it doesn\'t seem like it. Oh well, it\'ll probably make a really nice shield."};
descriptions["19450"]={cn:"卡波克用来防止制造机械鸦的时候烧坏自己的胡子。",en:"Kabrok used this to keep from burning his beard while performing various welds on the Korbot."};
descriptions["19451"]={cn:"能够抵挡酷热，也能预防脚臭。",en:"Boots that help protect from ultra strong heat, but also increase foot odor."};
descriptions["19453"]={cn:"卡波克用它来校准机械鸦。虽然破旧不堪，但仍然很好用。",en:"Kabrok used it to calibrate the Korbot down to the milimeter. It\'s very worn, but still functional."};
descriptions["19454"]={cn:"装入机械鸦使其能够减速并停下来。看上去很新的样子。",en:"These pads are used in the Korbot so that it can slow down and stop itself when moving about. They look new - extras, no doubt."};
descriptions["19455"]={cn:"如果持有的时间过长，这把铲子会吸收你体内的精华。由于魔力太大，不单独贩卖。",en:"If it\'s held onto for too long, this shovel exhausts the body and drains it of its vital energy. The item, judged too dangerous, is not sold in stores."};
descriptions["19456"]={cn:"这个配方会教你学会制作萨弗基亚海鲜汤。",en:"This scroll will teach you the recipe for See-Food Pie a la Sufokia"};
descriptions["19457"]={cn:"人工徽章被植入了机械鸦中，使系统变为全自动并且给予它一定的人工智能。",en:"Artificial Insignia that\'s inferior to that implemented in the Korbot. Makes a system autonomous and gives it an intelligent aspect."};
descriptions["19458"]={cn:"这个配方会教你学会制作清蒸啾啾。",en:"This scroll will teach you the recipe for Roast Crown of Piwi"};
descriptions["19459"]={cn:"这个配方会教你学会制作至尊虫虫披萨。",en:"This scroll will teach you the recipe for Fhenrat\'s Pizz\'larva"};
descriptions["19460"]={cn:"这个配方会教你学会制作喵布丁。",en:"This scroll will teach you the recipe for Bow Meow Paté"};
descriptions["19461"]={cn:"这个配方会教你学会制作绵球麻辣烫。",en:"This scroll will teach you the recipe for Sweet and Sour Gobball Stew"};
descriptions["19462"]={cn:"这个配方会教你学会制作酥脆绵球。",en:"This scroll will teach you the recipe for Crunchy Gobball Stew"};
descriptions["19463"]={cn:"这个配方会教你学会制作清蒸绵球。",en:"This scroll will teach you the recipe for Gooey Gobball Stew"};
descriptions["19464"]={cn:"这个配方会教你学会制作绵球糊。",en:"This scroll will teach you the recipe for Breaded Gobball Stew"};
descriptions["19465"]={cn:"这个配方会教你学会制作豆芙麦片。",en:"This scroll will teach you the recipe for Mashed Potatofu with Corn"};
descriptions["19466"]={cn:"这个配方会教你学会制作腌豆芙。",en:"This scroll will teach you the recipe for Marinated Mashed Potatofu"};
descriptions["19467"]={cn:"这个配方会教你学会制作酸甜豆芙。",en:"This scroll will teach you the recipe for Sweet Mashed Potatofu"};
descriptions["19468"]={cn:"这个配方会教你学会制作辣豆芙。",en:"This scroll will teach you the recipe for Mashed Potatofu with Spices"};
descriptions["19469"]={cn:"这个配方会教你学会制作布拉克玛烧味。",en:"This scroll will teach you the recipe for Brakmarian Stohlen"};
descriptions["19470"]={cn:"这个配方会教你学会制作阿玛克纳野味砂锅。",en:"This scroll will teach you the recipe for Amaknian Cassaroll"};
descriptions["19471"]={cn:"这个配方会教你学会制作邦塔提拉米苏。",en:"This scroll will teach you the recipe for Bontarian Tiramisoup"};
descriptions["19472"]={cn:"乌鸦嘴是乌鸦的嘴，是鸦人传统美食的佐料。基本采用大块的乌鸦和许多神秘的原料 - 每个鸦人有自己独特的配方，经过世世代代的流传变成这样。",en:"An old term, now outdated, corbeak is the beak of a Crobak, an ingredient in this traditional Raskaw dish. It starts with large pieces of Crobak and mysterious and varied spices - and each Krobelle has their own personal, secret recipe. It\'s passed from mother to daughter and improved over generations."};
descriptions["19473"]={cn:"这个配方会教你学会制作清蒸灰乌鸦。",en:"This scroll will teach you the recipe for Raskaw Crobeak Fricassee"};
descriptions["19487"]={cn:"敢不敢捡起来，放进包里？",en:"Don\'t keep it in your bag too long, or you\'ll find yourself covered in a nauseating and unshakable stench."};
descriptions["19488"]={cn:"近期发现的一种基因。很显然能够把村民变成食屍鬼，被广泛应用於某种邪恶实验。",en:"This gene was discovered quite recently. Apparently, it transforms villagers into something other than Ghouls, and is used for some rather morbid experiments."};
descriptions["19489"]={cn:"恐惧之情溢于言表。",en:"Your fear shall be forever written upon your face."};
descriptions["19490"]={cn:"一二三，跟你走。",en:"Once you tie them on, these giant paws will follow you anywhere you go."};
descriptions["19491"]={cn:"毛茸茸的，引领时尚潮流。",en:"Brushed against the fur and sporting a magnificent bushy tail, this fur will make the fashionistas happy."};
descriptions["19492"]={cn:"在你的肩膀上安顿下来，让你不那么慌张。",en:"Resting gently on your shoulders, the hands serve as a big comfort when you\'re taking risks."};
descriptions["19493"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["19494"]={cn:"有着巨大的低胸领口，让刚站起来的尸体看起来更恐怖。",en:"A vest with a plunging neckline, guaranteed to look stunning on your newly reanimated corpse."};
descriptions["19495"]={cn:"僵尸舞会上的流行款，让硬朗的线条显出柔美的身姿。",en:"Very popular with our non-living friends, these rags allow for some pretty fluid movements, depending on the rigidity of the body in question."};
descriptions["19496"]={cn:"虽然运气不好，关键时刻还是能救你的小命。",en:"Although unlucky, this paw can repel several enemies and save your skin."};
descriptions["19497"]={cn:"就好像握着有一双无形的手，想一想就觉得可怕。",en:"When you think about it, it\'s almost as if you\'re holding hands with the unfortunate former owner of these fingers."};
descriptions["19498"]={cn:"前往地下城门口的兑奖机处兑换酷炫的奖励。",en:"Use the machine across from the dungeon to exchange your tokens for fantastic rewards."};
descriptions["19499"]={cn:"点击两下来把整组古代资源转换成新的资源。古代资源需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["19500"]={cn:"粗制滥造的东西。",en:"This rather unattractive fur was ripped off with much fuss and hard work."};
descriptions["19501"]={cn:"维多利亚·爱因斯坦实验室的第一件作品，采用了最新的锁骨和肩胛骨制成。销量很差劲。",en:"One of Victoria-Franka\'s first experiments, using a clavicle and a scapula, which didn\'t quite turn out."};
descriptions["19502"]={cn:"正好配得上你这双老脚。",en:"Comfortable boots for old painful feet."};
descriptions["19503"]={cn:"紧紧绷绷的东西。",en:"Experiments work best when the subject is well restrained! And the team survives."};
descriptions["19504"]={cn:"华而不实的东西。",en:"The purpose these chains serve is more decorative than functional."};
descriptions["19505"]={cn:"冬凉夏暖的东西。",en:"This shawl really keeps you warm in the summer - and cold in the winter."};
descriptions["19506"]={cn:"虚有其表的东西。",en:"An inexpensive way to compensate for your premature baldness."};
descriptions["19507"]={cn:"俗不可耐的东西。",en:"This necklace, engraved with Kiki, is a perfect indication of all the affection this abomination\'s owner has for it."};
descriptions["19508"]={cn:"她从浴室的窗口爬进来...",en:"She came in through the bathroom window, protected by a Shildodeth..."};
descriptions["19509"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["19513"]={cn:"纪念你曾经切碎过一只邪恶的蘑菇。",en:"A battle trophy to remind you of your victory in the dungeon."};
descriptions["19514"]={cn:"纪念你曾经切碎过一只邪恶的蘑菇。",en:"A battle trophy to remind you of your victory in the dungeon."};
descriptions["19515"]={cn:"在你的庇护袋里看上去很完美。",en:"This miniature will look perfect in your Haven Bag."};
descriptions["19516"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few drops should suffice."};
descriptions["19518"]={cn:"源自古老的家族，高品质的保证。",en:"This sword, created from unidentifiable bones is decorated with the forearm of a decrepit Borbat."};
descriptions["19519"]={cn:"就算现在，我依旧可以像切乳酪一样把你们...",en:"Pierce putrid flesh like butter, with one swift stroke!"};
descriptions["19520"]={cn:"效果不错，使用前先看说明书。",en:"Quite handy for dealing with the undead."};
descriptions["19521"]={cn:"这把刀藏在裤子口袋里，未免略大了一点吧。",en:"Even though it\'s heavy and a bit too thick for your pockets, this dagger is indispensable when it comes to cutting through bone."};
descriptions["19522"]={cn:"这件武器用来对付渣妈妈的试验品。",en:"This weapon is used to take apart Madame Enstein\'s experimental victims. Mostly it\'s used for \"detail work\"."};
descriptions["19523"]={cn:"腿骨和胫骨做成的武器，丢在街上会引来汪汪。",en:"This weapon is made of two parts: a femur and a tibia. Which should catch the interest of pretty much any Bow Wows or Boowolves in the area."};
descriptions["19525"]={cn:"[ADMIN] 牛逼的翻译是不需要女朋友的。",en:"\"Ash nazg durbatulûk, ash nazg gimbatul, Ash nazg thrakatulûk agh burzum-ishi krimpatul.\" Got that? Good."};
descriptions["19527"]={cn:"[ADMIN] 天啊...这根本不是真正的约翰！也不是真正的囧...",en:"[ADMIN] And it\'s not even a real False Renaud!!! Frankly, something\'s screwy here..."};
descriptions["19528"]={cn:"[ADMIN] 天啊...这根本不是真正的约翰！",en:"[ADMIN] It\'s not even a real Renaud Ring..."};
descriptions["19529"]={cn:"[ADMIN] 三重疾病 = 疾病缠身！",en:"[ADMIN] Triplesicks = haxortrix!"};
descriptions["19530"]={cn:"[ADMIN] 约翰是字幕组的成员，成天码字吐槽。这个戒指让他无槽可吐。",en:"[ADMIN] Renaud wanted more fingers to type faster. He wanted more Wakfu to outsmart all his WP costs. So he made a ring that gave him everything."};
descriptions["19531"]={cn:"能力越大，责任越大。",en:"With great power comes great responsibility."};
descriptions["19532"]={cn:"能力越大，责任越大。",en:"With great power comes great responsibility."};
descriptions["19534"]={cn:"[ADMIN] 用这把匕首你可以将敌人（包括盟友）逼向绝境。他们总是说...好事总是慢慢来的。",en:"[ADMIN] With this magnificent dagger you can put your enemies (and allies!) at death\'s door. So they say... good things come in small packages"};
