descriptions["19543"]={cn:"这件华丽的时装在狼群中有相当大的影响力。",en:"This magnificent costume has a great effect at Boowerewolf parties with friends."};
descriptions["19544"]={cn:"许多人都对这件时装羡慕嫉妒恨。穿着这件时装，你想叫就叫，想咬就咬。",en:"You\'ll make lots of people jealous with this costume. It\'s basically a free pass to growl and bit as much as you want."};
descriptions["19545"]={cn:"穿着这件覆盖着真正的狼牙的铁肩甲，你会变得相当犀利！",en:"You\'ll look sharp wearing these iron epaulettes covered in real Boowolf fangs!"};
descriptions["19546"]={cn:"用狼牙装饰的铁质重甲。",en:"A heavy iron breastplate with Boowolf fang decoration."};
descriptions["19547"]={cn:"非常适合搬砖时穿着。",en:"Perfect for scratching out a living."};
descriptions["19548"]={cn:"这双镀铁加固的鞋子非常耐用。",en:"These iron-plated reinforced clawed boots are very durable."};
descriptions["19549"]={cn:"穿着表面覆盖着剃刀般锋利的牙齿的令人生畏的肩甲，没有人愿意在你肩上哭泣。",en:"Formidable epaulettes covered in razor-sharp teeth. No one will want to cry on your shoulder with these on."};
descriptions["19550"]={cn:"野蛮的样子来展现你狂野的一面！",en:"A savage look to express your wild side!"};
descriptions["19551"]={cn:"野蛮，凶猛，令人印象深刻。",en:"An impressive, savage and barbaric helm."};
descriptions["19552"]={cn:"极具魄力的重甲，使用了铁和狼毛强化。",en:"A heavy and imposing breastplate, reinforced with iron and fur."};
descriptions["19553"]={cn:"毛皮与金属完美结合，提供终极的保护和舒适度。",en:"Fur-lined and reinforced with metal, the ultimate in protection and comfort."};
descriptions["19554"]={cn:"质量上乘的毛绒披风，尔夫的最爱！",en:"A quality cloak and furry attractive!"};
descriptions["19555"]={cn:"擅于和一群敌人作战的狼。",en:"A Boowolf trained to fight groups of enemies."};
descriptions["19556"]={cn:"擅于和敌人远距离作战的狼。",en:"A Boowolf trained to fight from a distance."};
descriptions["19557"]={cn:"擅于和敌人近距离作战的狼。",en:"A boowolf specialized in the art of melee fighting."};
descriptions["19558"]={cn:"擅于和敌人一对一作战的狼。",en:"A Boowolf trained to fight against a single enemy."};
descriptions["19560"]={cn:"可以装备于狼，成为真正的兽群领袖。",en:"This Boowolf skin will make you the leader of the pack."};
