descriptions["19568"]={cn:"我们都过着脸谱一样的人生。",en:"Lets one, at a glance, get info about your overbooked character."};
descriptions["19569"]={cn:"人靠衣装才能威风。",en:"The clothes may not make the man, but they may make you a warrior."};
descriptions["19570"]={cn:"让你拥有一股冷嗖嗖的气场和一群神叨叨的信徒。",en:"This costume will give you the air of an inhuman beauty and of being linked to a certain sanguine sect."};
descriptions["19571"]={cn:"源自樱花之乡的设计，能为穿戴者带来天长地久的幸福生活。",en:"This cherry-tree design costume is supposed to bestow a long and happy life on whoever wears it."};
descriptions["19572"]={cn:"穿上这套衣服你就厉害啦？并不。",en:"This costume won\'t make you a prodigy!"};
descriptions["19573"]={cn:"从现在的样子来看，这只咕咕恶贯满盈，死期已至。",en:"Given the way it looks now, this Googoo\'s devious days are over!"};
descriptions["19574"]={cn:"我即时间。",en:"Time is the great equalizer."};
descriptions["19575"]={cn:"穿越冰原的必备装备。",en:"Absolutely essential for little walks across the icy lands."};
