descriptions["19660"]={cn:"不要用力摩擦这羊毛，它实在太硬了。谁会知道奥铎门徒们会拿它做什么。",en:"Don\'t rub too hard against this fleece, it\'s very hard. Who knows what Otomai\'s Disciples will use it for."};
descriptions["19661"]={cn:"这件文物被发现于阿玛克纳，称为奥利哈刚，是打开萨弗基亚海底神庙的三把钥匙之一，供奉着欧塔波达神，是欧萨莫达神存在的形式之一。",en:"This ancient relic was found in Amakna. This Orichalcum is one of the three \"keys\" that can be used to open the Sunken Temple of Sufokia, the former place of worship of the god Oktapodas, one of the god Osamodas\' forms."};
descriptions["19662"]={cn:"这件文物被发现于邦塔，称为奥利哈刚，是打开萨弗基亚海底神庙的三把钥匙之一，供奉着欧塔波达神，是欧萨莫达神存在的形式之一。",en:"This Relic of Antiquity was found in Bonta. This Orichalcum is one of the three \"keys\" that can be used to open the Sunken Temple of Sufokia, the former place of worship of the god Oktapodas, one of the god Osamodas\' forms."};
descriptions["19663"]={cn:"这件文物被发现于布拉克玛，称为奥利哈刚，是打开萨弗基亚海底神庙的三把钥匙之一，供奉着欧塔波达神，是欧萨莫达神存在的形式之一。",en:"This Relic of Antiquity was found in Brakmar. This Orichalcum is one of the three \"keys\" that can be used to open the Sunken Temple of Sufokia, the former place of worship of the god Oktapodas, one of the god Osamodas\' forms."};
descriptions["19664"]={cn:"这尊漂亮的石绵鲍威雕像适合放置在你的洞穴里。",en:"This delightful miniature of Bovis the Rockwooled will look wonderful in your cave."};
descriptions["19665"]={cn:"这东西相当古老，其真实性和实际用途只能由考古学砖家来鉴定。",en:"This object is really quite ancient. Only an expert archaosologist can verify its authenticity and usefulness."};
descriptions["19667"]={cn:"前往地下城门口的兑奖机处兑换酷炫的奖励。",en:"Use the machine across from the dungeon to exchange your tokens for fantastic rewards."};
descriptions["19668"]={cn:"完成正式英雄测试的称号奖励！",en:"A title for those who have completed the Half-Hero tests."};
descriptions["19669"]={cn:"自带治疗功能，无比实用！",en:"The most practical Haven Bag when first-aid is required after an accident!"};
descriptions["19670"]={cn:"当你厌倦了传送来传送去的生活，就会知道家的好处。",en:"If you\'re wiped after a long day of creating portals, go have a rest in your peaceful Haven."};
descriptions["19671"]={cn:"神明创造的十二世界一直都很安静，直到奥铎曼创造了小奥古。",en:"\"The Gods created the World of Twelve and it was quiet. Otomai created Ogrest and it never was again.\""};
descriptions["19694"]={cn:"有人说,汉尼芭背后有眼睛,当你看到这件披风,你就会明白为什么。",en:"They say that Kanniballs have eyes in the back of their heads. You\'ll understand why when you see this cape!"};
descriptions["19695"]={cn:"尽量不要把这面具弄坏了，如果真的坏了，你可以随时用胶水粘好它。",en:"Try not to break this, but if you do, you can always patch it together with masking tape."};
descriptions["19696"]={cn:"汉尼芭舞厅的最佳拍档！",en:"These epaulettes look great on the dance floor of the Kanniballroom!"};
descriptions["19697"]={cn:"与人握手的时候，手环可以帮你把别人手捏碎！",en:"This bracelet provides substantial support when shaking hands with someone really vigorously."};
descriptions["19698"]={cn:"哆嗦木戒来自一位搁浅的水手，他的老帆船失事了。被发现的时候他嘴里嘟嚷着什么“木材”和“哆嗦”，这枚戒指因此而得名。",en:"The Shiver Ring was found on a stranded sailor after his old schooner was shipwrecked. He was found muttering something about \"timbers\" and \"shiver\", which is how the ring got its name."};
descriptions["19699"]={cn:"为了纪念月亮岛最高的、唯一的山而打碟，额不，打造的。",en:"This Talisman was created in honor of the highest—and only—mountain on Moon Island."};
descriptions["19700"]={cn:"Long worn by the grouchiest Kanniball in the village, it now belongs to the grumpiest adventurer.",en:"Long worn by the grouchiest Kanniball in the village, it now belongs to the grumpiest adventurer."};
descriptions["19701"]={cn:"由于汉尼芭食人族习惯于赤脚走路，他们直到冬天才会发现鞋子不见了。",en:"As they are accustomed to walking barefoot, the Kanniball to whom these shoes belonged will not notice they\'re missing until winter."};
descriptions["19702"]={cn:"正是你在阳光沙滩休息时需要的。",en:"Just what you need when relaxing on the beach at sunset."};
descriptions["19703"]={cn:"穿上这件衬衣，温度会上升，但是不会变热，如果你知道我的意思！",en:"With this shirt, temperatures will rise, but it won\'t get hotter, if you know what I mean!"};
descriptions["19704"]={cn:"避免肩膀晒黑最好的方法是穿上这对肩甲。",en:"Wearing these is the best way of avoiding sunburnt shoulders."};
descriptions["19705"]={cn:"适合晒太阳时穿着。但是，跳舞的时候不建议穿着，因为它几乎没有遮住任何东西！",en:"Perfect for basking in the sun. However, dancing in it is not recommended because it barely covers anything!"};
descriptions["19706"]={cn:"只要你能早点意识到，你可以利用椰树叶子制作一个有用的帽子来防止阳光直射眼睛，你才不会一开始就在这种悲惨的小岛迷路了。",en:"If only you\'d realized earlier that you could fashion a useful hat from a Kokonut tree to protect your eyes from the sun, you would never have got lost on this wretched island in the first place."};
descriptions["19707"]={cn:"你可能会误以为这个披风由椰树叶制成的，但事实并非如此...真的，相信我！",en:"You could be forgiven for thinking this cape was made from a Koko leaf, but it\'s not true... Honestly, trust me!"};
descriptions["19708"]={cn:"这双鞋会让你的敌人感受到恐惧。",en:"Sporting these sandals will give your enemies a sense of dread."};
descriptions["19709"]={cn:"你可以用这些小花瓶装饰抖椰人，去参加月亮岛盛装舞会。记住要倒入琥珀柑香酒，切忌加水！",en:"You can attach these tiny vases to Kokolerics as pretty ornaments for their Full Moon Parties. Just fill with amber Curaçao. Do not fill with water!"};
descriptions["19710"]={cn:"这枚戒指并没有那么强力，但是它是如此的微不足道，所以没人想偷走它。",en:"This ring isn\'t very powerful, but it\'s so full of splinters that no one will steal it off you."};
descriptions["19711"]={cn:"每一个勇敢的冒险者，时不时地需要脖子上戴着这样的项链，手上拿着鸡尾酒。",en:"Every bold adventurer needs a flower garland around your neck and a cocktail in your hand from time to time."};
descriptions["19712"]={cn:"胸甲的名字虽然可笑，却意外的结实。毕竟是纯植物材料制成，品质杠杠滴。",en:"This amusingly named breastplate is surprisingly strong considering it\'s made from nothing but plant matter."};
descriptions["19713"]={cn:"曾经拥有这个肩甲的水手已消失在海洋中那片神秘海域，它一定是在这儿被冲上了月亮岛。即便如此，直到现在那名水手依旧杳无音讯。",en:"This nice pair of floral-themed shoulder guards are perfect for island strolls, or brutal fights with monsters."};
descriptions["19714"]={cn:"毕格·汀克是一位著名的探险家，他探索了许许多多十二世界的未知洞穴，却在探索月亮岛的任务中失联了。",en:"Biggs Tinker was a popular adventurer who explored many caves around the World of Twelve. He disappeared on a mission to Moon Island."};
descriptions["19715"]={cn:"装饰着来自月亮岛地下的金片片，只是金片片！有人喜欢戴这顶帽子，因为可以用它闪瞎敌人的狗眼。不过在地穴中它可不会自己发光！",en:"Decorated with gold pieces found in the depths of Moon Island, some use this hat and its shiny bits to blind their enemies. No, it doesn\'t work in caves."};
descriptions["19716"]={cn:"这披风穿着不是很舒服，但有着能让他人尊重你个人空间的优势。",en:"This cape is not very comfortable to wear, but has the advantage of making sure others respect your personal space."};
descriptions["19717"]={cn:"高等汉尼草叶纤维精制而成。除了防滑之外，这些靴子可不是吃素的。",en:"Made from the fibers of Kannivore leaves, these boots are non-slip and non-vegan."};
descriptions["19718"]={cn:"这个戒指有数百年的历史。但是没人知道具体是几百年，或许我们需要在显微镜下研究研究才能告诉你答案。",en:"This ring is hundreds of years old. Unfortunately no one can tell how old without a microscope."};
descriptions["19719"]={cn:"戴着这指环超过一年，你的手指可能会有所损伤。不过，如果婚姻不幸，也许这指环反而对你是有益的。",en:"Wearing this ring for longer than a year will result in the loss of the finger wearing it. This could be beneficial if you\'re in an unhappy marriage!"};
descriptions["19720"]={cn:"绑着护符的丝线有时会在携带者的脖子上收紧，最终导致意识丧失。",en:"The cord holding this talisman can sometimes tighten around the wearer\'s neck, ultimately causing a loss of consciousness."};
descriptions["19724"]={cn:"只有每日之星才能骑上这令人印象深刻的坐骑。它突出的肌肉筋脉塑造了完美的体形。",en:"Only a Meridian Star can claim to ride this impressive mount. Its rippling muscles cut an imposing figure."};
descriptions["19725"]={cn:"只有每日之星才能骑上这令人印象深刻的坐骑。它突出的肌肉筋脉塑造了完美的体形。",en:"Only a Meridian Star can claim to ride this impressive mount. Its rippling muscles cut an imposing figure."};
descriptions["19726"]={cn:"只有每日之星才能骑上这令人印象深刻的坐骑。它突出的肌肉筋脉塑造了完美的体形。",en:"Only a Meridian Star can claim to ride this impressive mount. Its rippling muscles cut an imposing figure."};
descriptions["19728"]={cn:"这件时装是每日之神徽章的复制品，不带加成。",en:"This costume is a copy of the Meridia Insignia, but holds no power."};
descriptions["19730"]={cn:"有了这套时装，你能永远都保持一副鬼脸了！",en:"With this costume, you\'ll always be making a face!"};
descriptions["19731"]={cn:"很明显，你已经训练有素了，能拉雪橇啦！",en:"You\'ve clearly been well trained to pull a sleigh!"};
descriptions["19733"]={cn:"原力与你同在！",en:"Because the force is with you!"};
descriptions["19734"]={cn:"想把一千零一爪弄锋利的人专用。",en:"For anyone who wants to sharpen their thousand and one paws."};
descriptions["19735"]={cn:"燃烧吧，我的小宇宙！",en:"Let your inner animosity out."};
descriptions["19736"]={cn:"雪人令我们回忆起小时候的美好时光，多么温馨啊。",en:"A snowman to make you nostalgic. It\'s nice."};
descriptions["19737"]={cn:"它足以令你毛骨悚然。真的！",en:"It\'s enough to make your blood run cold. Literally!"};
descriptions["19738"]={cn:"小心！别溅太多血在上面！",en:"Careful not to spill too much blood on it!"};
descriptions["19739"]={cn:"比起来帮你出谋划策，这只小猴猴更愿意给你添点乱。你确定你想要那样的悲惨经历？",en:"More mischievous than intelligent, this little monkey will give you a hard time."};
descriptions["19740"]={cn:"宠物染料可以于宠物设定介面中更改。此物品已无用处，可以将其分解掉。",en:"Pet colorings can be changed in the pet settings interface. This item is obsolete; you can recycle it."};
descriptions["19742"]={cn:"这个特别的装饰可以给战斗绵球穿上，在万圣节去吓吓那些小学生！",en:"A Gobball War Chief skin that is sure to scare children!"};
descriptions["19743"]={cn:"你值得拥有这个大图腾！",en:"You\'re proud of your big totem."};
descriptions["19744"]={cn:"当你用光蜡烛的时候，驯鹿可以用作应急灯。",en:"This reindeer can also serve as an emergency light if you happen to run out of candles."};
descriptions["19745"]={cn:"你要告诫自己提防着那些椰子，尤其是大的那个。",en:"You\'re often told you should watch out for Kokos, especially the big ones."};
descriptions["19746"]={cn:"相传在古时候，一位当时最有名的凯拉，制作了风语腰带。但是，这一个很可能只是由汉尼芭走私者带来的劣质复制品。",en:"According to legend, the Belt of the Winds was created a long time ago by the most popular Cra. But this one is probably just an inferior copy slapped together by a Kanniball smuggler."};
descriptions["19748"]={cn:"艾卡菲利丢了这块肥皂，捡起来你就到神域了！",en:"This kibble, offered to visitors by Ecaflips, will take you to Ecaflipus in an instant!"};
descriptions["19749"]={cn:"放置于黑暗之中的时候，要点灯才找得到。",en:"This carbon is very hard to see in the dark, even if you\'re using a lantern."};
descriptions["19750"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["19751"]={cn:"如果不是因为有“琥珀酒”，我们不得不把啤酒叫做“棕黄色发酵液”了。",en:"If it weren\'t for \"amber nectar,\" we\'d have to call beer a \"brownish-yellow fermented liquid.\""};
descriptions["19752"]={cn:"看！一只远古滋滋被困在这琥珀中了！ 我想知道能否提取出DNA...",en:"Oh look, an ancient Moskito trapped in some prehistoric amber. I wonder if we could extract some DNA..."};
descriptions["19753"]={cn:"这些树枝在月之沙滩里生长地意外的好。",en:"This cutting takes well when planted in Moon Beach soil."};
descriptions["19754"]={cn:"椰树虽因椰子而闻名，但是它柔软而坚固的木板也是十分有用的。",en:"Kokonut palms are great for their Kokonuts, but the supple and robust planks it also provides are very useful too."};
descriptions["19755"]={cn:"这种椰木来自于古老的莲椰木，获得了木匠们的极高赞誉。",en:"This Kokonut tree wood comes from the original Kokos Nucifera, the most majestic of them all. It is prized by artisans for its exceptional qualities."};
descriptions["19756"]={cn:"这些树枝在月之沙滩里生长地意外的好。",en:"This cutting takes well when planted in Moon Beach soil."};
descriptions["19757"]={cn:"独特的纤维结构，适合做皮革。也可以作为临时避难用，无需额外加工。",en:"This wood has unique fibers, used for making leather. It\'s also useful as a temporary shelter as-is; no work required."};
descriptions["19758"]={cn:"与基友双飞的最佳伴侣。",en:"This wood is perfect for sharing between friends."};
descriptions["19759"]={cn:"你能让我静静吗？我只想静静的游一会！大海那么大还不够你游吗？小伙子，你484sa？你到底想干嘛？你想打架？唉，真是服了你了！",en:"Can you let me go? I\'d really like to swim in peace! The ocean not big enough for you, that it? You have a problem, little one? What\'s wrong with you? You wanna fight? Oh, yeah, I\'m real impressed!"};
descriptions["19760"]={cn:"好吧，我知道有一个笑话。嗯，有一个贝壳大师，看到了吗？他走到海里，好吧，他不是用走的，他游进去。嗯，其实软体动物是不会动的。他总是在一个地方，然后爱鱿，额，他们...我搞混了。那应该是一个黑贝壳和旗鱼，他们都没有走，然后什么都没发生...忘了吧...",en:"All right, I know one joke. Um, there\'s a Master Mussel, see? And he walks up to a sea, well he doesn\'t walk up, he swims up. Well, actually the mollusk isn\'t moving. He\'s in one place and then the Kralove, well they... I mixed up. There was a Darth Mussel and a Zordfish. None of them were walking, so forget that..."};
descriptions["19761"]={cn:"虽然个头小了点，但是伦家还是凯门鳄啊，很流弊的好不好！",en:"It may only be a dwarf species, but catching a caiman is still a feat to brag about!"};
descriptions["19762"]={cn:"抓到这只凯门鳄后，追逐着你听到的奇怪的滴答声，你觉得你在远处看到了一艘海盗船。",en:"After catching this Caiman, you thought you saw a pirate ship in the distance, chasing this strange Tick-Tock sound you can hear."};
descriptions["19763"]={cn:"这些种子在月之沙滩里生长地意外的好。",en:"This seed takes well when planted in Moon Beach soil."};
descriptions["19764"]={cn:"有了这个，你离棕榈杯超级碗的冠军就只剩下一步之遥了。不过，现在你应该关心的是，拿着这个你能在水里游的更快吗？",en:"You were so close to winning the Palm d\'Or. But you\'ll just have to be happy with this item, which will help you move faster in the water."};
descriptions["19765"]={cn:"是的！你是赢家！一个大写的好极了！",en:"Yep! You\'re the winner! A huge bravo!"};
descriptions["19767"]={cn:"这些种子在月之沙滩里生长地意外的好。",en:"These seeds grow amazingly well in the ground around Moon Beach."};
descriptions["19768"]={cn:"这苦木薯不能直接食用，它需要加工干燥，或做成面粉才可以使用它。",en:"This tuberous root cannot be eaten as is. It needs to be dried and processed, or made into flour, before it can be used."};
descriptions["19769"]={cn:"木薯可甜啦，可以直接吃。但是作为一种蔬菜，最好是去皮煮熟了再吃。",en:"This Maniok is sweet and can be eaten as-is. To eat it as a vegetable, it is best to peel and boil it first."};
descriptions["19770"]={cn:"这些种子在月之丛林里生长地意外的好。",en:"This seed takes well when planted in Moon Jungle soil."};
descriptions["19771"]={cn:"甜甜的香味，实际上并不是那么美好的甜，如过你不小心戴着这些花的话...",en:"Sweet-smelling, but not so sweet if you\'re not careful wearing these flowers."};
descriptions["19772"]={cn:"你的自我价值的象征，爱似乎随风漂浮在空中。",en:"A symbol of your self-worth, love seems to float through the air, thanks to the Winds."};
descriptions["19773"]={cn:"这些种子在月之丛林里生长地意外的好。",en:"This seed takes well when planted in Moon Jungle soil."};
descriptions["19774"]={cn:"日光百合会让你感到和百合一样清新。",en:"This Day Lily will make you feel as fresh as a Lily."};
descriptions["19775"]={cn:"这朵花在夜里会发出荧光，但遗憾的是，没有月光的时候人们根本看不到它。",en:"This flower looks stunning at night, which is a shame because no one can see it in the dark."};
descriptions["19776"]={cn:"点击两下来把整组古代资源转换成新的资源。古代资源需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["19777"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["19778"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
