descriptions["19780"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["19781"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["19782"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["19783"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["19784"]={cn:"这种树皮来自一种很普通的热带椰树，没啥特别的。",en:"This bark was from a common Tropikoko. It holds no special value."};
descriptions["19785"]={cn:"这颗椰子经常受伤，孕育在其中的憎恶和愤怒将成为它强大的武器。",en:"This Tropikoko Nut has been traumatized so many times that the hatred it harbors inside makes it extremely powerful."};
descriptions["19786"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few grains should suffice."};
descriptions["19787"]={cn:"如果你故意被抓了，用这个可以掩藏你的谦逊，尽管我并不觉得你有那种品质。",en:"If ever you\'re caught as nature intended, you could try to use of these to hide your modesty. Although it really depends on how immodest you\'re being."};
descriptions["19790"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["19791"]={cn:"总想认识真正的椰人·坚果？现在你有这个机会了。",en:"You\'ve always wanted to get to know the real Koko the Nutt, now you can."};
descriptions["19792"]={cn:"像哈利波特那样挥挥魔杖然后高声念出咒语“烈焰熊熊”，这根魔杖会引来烈火并发生爆炸。 倒霉的巫师卡彻·艾道福曾经这么玩过一次，那时魔杖还插在他的腰带上呢。",en:"If you vigorously shake this staff, it will start giving off sparks and eventually explode. The unfortunate Kutcher Endoff once went running with it still attached to his belt..."};
descriptions["19793"]={cn:"你用力过猛了，戴上这裂开的面具比不戴更糟糕。",en:"You hit a bit too hard. This mask is cracked and wearing it would be worse than not wearing it."};
descriptions["19794"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few grains should suffice."};
descriptions["19795"]={cn:"你从毛茸茸的汉尼芭身上得到了它们。",en:"You must have got these from a pair of hairy Kanniballs."};
descriptions["19796"]={cn:"可以在下列兑奖机使用此奖章兑换奖励：热带椰子、食人藤、食人族、尼罗鳄、忤逆熊猫、沙鼠。",en:"Use the following machines to exchange your tokens for fantastic rewards: Tropikoko, Kanniball, Kannivore, Crocodyl, Pandissident, Gerbean."};
descriptions["19797"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["19798"]={cn:"这粗糙又冰冷的触感，很难相信让人相信这毛发属于活人。",en:"These hairs are rough and cold to the touch. It\'s hard to believe they belonged to anything living."};
descriptions["19799"]={cn:"你所有的制造物和材料都能放进这篮子里！",en:"This basket lets you put away all your refinements and components!"};
descriptions["19800"]={cn:"曾有人说这是有史以来最最伟大的长矛，现在看来这说法略有夸大。",en:"Once revered as the greatest lance ever, its performance has since proven to be artificially enhanced."};
descriptions["19801"]={cn:"真加王以前最爱用这只吹箭给他的敌人们爆菊了！",en:"Gengas Kin\'s favorite pastime to is to shoot darts into his enemies\' behinds with this Blowpipe."};
