descriptions["19855"]={cn:"相传在古时候，一位当时最有名的凯拉，制作了风语腰带。但是，这一个很可能只是由汉尼芭走私者带来的劣质复制品。",en:"According to legend, the Belt of the Winds was created a long time ago by the most popular Cra. But this one is probably just an inferior copy slapped together by a Kanniball smuggler."};
descriptions["19856"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Portable, easy to assemble, and ideal for all those unforeseeable moments, from setting off on adventures to picnics with the mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["19857"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Portable, easy to assemble, and ideal for all those unforeseeable moments, from setting off on adventures to picnics with the mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["19858"]={cn:"当日落时，记住当地这句充满智慧的口诀：“润唇膏，棕榈魔力，没有伤害。”",en:"When the sun\'s beating down, remember this wise mantra spoken by the locals: \"lip balm, palm charm, no harm.\""};
descriptions["19859"]={cn:"这会让你的肩膀更加美味。",en:"These will make your shoulders look extremely tasty."};
descriptions["19862"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Portable, easy to assemble, and ideal for all those unforeseeable moments, from setting off on adventures to picnics with the mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["19863"]={cn:"你总是做梦想成为超级英雄；好吧，穿上这件披风你就可以成为坚果侠了。",en:"You always wanted to be a superhero; well, now you can be Nuttman with this cape."};
descriptions["19864"]={cn:"出于某种原因，这个腰带比大多数常见的围在腰间的坚果带围的还要高。",en:"For some reason, this belt is worn higher than most the more common Round-the-Waist Nutt"};
descriptions["19865"]={cn:"赶紧拿这个蠢的不行头盔把你的榆木脑袋挡住。",en:"Cover your nut with this Nutte Covering."};
descriptions["19866"]={cn:"想和别人比赛打排球？丢掉这副手套吧！",en:"If you want to challenge someone to a game of beach volleyball, simply throw these down."};
descriptions["19867"]={cn:"在你玩月亮排球的时候，你需要这条绷带来保护你的手！因为球是用椰树做的！",en:"You need to protect your hands when playing Moon-volleyball because the ball is just a Kokonut!"};
descriptions["19868"]={cn:"在湿热的雨林里戴着这条槟榔渣织成的围巾，又清新又有型，一定很适合你！",en:"A refreshing and sparkling amulet for hot, humid days."};
descriptions["19869"]={cn:"小心点，你不想被弄疼的是吧？",en:"Careful when you handle these, you don\'t want to feel a prick."};
descriptions["19870"]={cn:"日落的肆候，穿着它在沙滩上围着篝火来支舞简直四，完美！",en:"These are perfect for thinging round the fire on the thand at thunthet."};
descriptions["19871"]={cn:"多么美妙的贴身胸甲！只有它才能展现我完美的身材！",en:"This plastron fights very snugly, perhaps too much so, but it really improves the figure!"};
descriptions["19872"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Portable, easy to assemble, and ideal for all those unforeseeable moments, from setting off on adventures to picnics with the mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["19873"]={cn:"纤维制成的披风，口感风味极佳，令人惊讶的美味。",en:"This cape is made of long strands of fiber, which are surprisingly tasty."};
descriptions["19874"]={cn:"教室角落里的熊孩子曾在学校戴过它，人们才发现这头盔在战斗中灰常顶用。",en:"Once used in schools for naughty children to wear in the corner of the classroom, it was discovered that this head covering was very useful in combat."};
descriptions["19875"]={cn:"这件衣服的制造者声称它可以阻止子弹，还没人敢检验这一说法。你敢吗？",en:"The maker of this garment claimed it could stop a bullet. No one has yet dared to test the claim. Would you?"};
descriptions["19876"]={cn:"这些手套怪模怪样的。",en:"These are some crazy-looking gloves."};
descriptions["19877"]={cn:"数数年轮，你就知道作为原料的那棵树长了多久了。",en:"You can always know how old this tree ring is."};
descriptions["19878"]={cn:"看啊看啊，这个护符黑得和AV嗨的心一样！",en:"Ah look, it matches the color of your heart!"};
descriptions["19879"]={cn:"不是非得围在腰间，用来运点东东也不错哒。",en:"Can be used for transporting items when not round one\'s waist."};
descriptions["19880"]={cn:"适合跳舞的鼓声...",en:"Perfect for dancing to the beat of the drum..."};
descriptions["19881"]={cn:"如果你穿上它，就别指望有人会和你肩并肩一起走了。",en:"With these, no one will want to go shoulder to shoulder with you."};
descriptions["19882"]={cn:"非常有用的武器，sala完了还能吃。",en:"A very useful tool, it has everything you need."};
descriptions["19883"]={cn:"这件盾牌能帮你抵挡闪电风暴。",en:"This will help to keep inclement weather off you."};
descriptions["19884"]={cn:"五毛一根，批发十根起，九折优惠啦！",en:"Just the tool you need for lopping the tops off Kokonuts, or any other type of nut."};
descriptions["19885"]={cn:"好好的汉子，说弯就弯了。",en:"Careful not to sit on this one."};
descriptions["19886"]={cn:"既实用，又是高贵的传统风俗，这件披风数世纪来在游牧民族中广受好评。",en:"Combining practicality and a respect for tradition, this Veil has been used by Nomads for centuries."};
descriptions["19887"]={cn:"除了在战斗中提供防护外，这副肩甲会在阳光下升温，提供额外的能量。",en:"As well as useful protection during combat, these epaulettes heat up in the sun and provide extra energy."};
descriptions["19888"]={cn:"游牧民族显著的标识，尽管他们怒火中烧也能凭着这个戒指分清自己人。",en:"A distinctive symbol that allows angry nomads to identify themselves."};
descriptions["19889"]={cn:"据说这枚戒指曾经属于一只红棕色的猴子， 我们都知道只有“阿猴”有那种颜色。不过你并不在乎，因为现在它归你了。",en:"It is said that this ring once belonged to a reddish-brown monkey. However, first of all, we all know that only Moogrrs can be this color, and secondly, you don\'t care because you have it now."};
descriptions["19890"]={cn:"讲道理，如果你真的饿了，你最好还是找点吃的填饱肚子，而不是勒紧裤腰带。",en:"This belt is now out of production, but was once the fastest commercial belt available."};
descriptions["19891"]={cn:"这件胸甲的正确用法是在沉船的时候把它垫在屁股底下，这样你就不会随着船一起沉没了。",en:"They say this chestpiece is unsinkable."};
descriptions["19892"]={cn:"丛林里不仅有令人战栗的危险，更有...泥巴。是的，这双靴子至少能让你远离泥泞的困扰。",en:"There are some terrifying dangers in the jungle. But it\'s also muddy, and these boots will at least protect you from that."};
descriptions["19893"]={cn:"Dofus里剑齿虎的牙齿怎么会出现在月亮岛，还被人做成了项链？有意思，真有意思。",en:"No one knows how a Sabredon tooth necklace ended up on Moon Island. But it\'s impressive nonetheless!"};
descriptions["19894"]={cn:"号令众生的至尊戒指！其实...你想太多了。",en:"The one ring to rule them all. No, honestly!"};
descriptions["19895"]={cn:"穿上这件护肩，你看上去仿佛变身成为了筋肉少年。注意：重点在“看上去”。",en:"These epaulettes will make your muscles seem huge, with an emphasis on \"seem.\""};
descriptions["19896"]={cn:"你想让我解释下这个面具的名字是什么意思吗？别做梦偷渡了！氪不改命，玄不救非！",en:"You really don\'t want to know where this mask got its name."};
descriptions["19897"]={cn:"欧洲细作卡卡！这根棒子会帮你打开新世界的大门！",en:"You can start a new life with this hammer."};
descriptions["19898"]={cn:"还在犹豫你为谁而战的立场吗？拿起它，没错的。",en:"The perfect shield for when you\'re deciding which side to fight for."};
descriptions["19899"]={cn:"这把武器深受一位名叫本·拉丁的椰人喜爱。",en:"Said to have been the preferred weapon of a certain Old Ben Kokonobi."};
descriptions["19900"]={cn:"这把匕首为了给自己取个炫酷的名字而操碎了心。",en:"This dagger is soul crushing."};
