descriptions["20013"]={cn:"变成一个图腾。开心时，站着。不开心，傻站着。",en:"As still as a totem."};
descriptions["20015"]={cn:"有了这个称号，你将能熟练地说出：“黑化肥发灰会挥发，灰化肥挥发会发黑”",en:"With this title, you will be able to proficiently say: \'Rubber baby buggie bumpers!\'"};
descriptions["20016"]={cn:"你的目标是星辰大海，然而你却来到了月亮岛。这个称号奖励给第一位到达200级的玩家。",en:"You chained them, now you shall be rewarded! This title is awarded because you were one of the first players to reach level 200."};
descriptions["20017"]={cn:"凯恩·卡卡艾斯的漂亮模型，绵球球冠军幽灵限定版。",en:"A beautiful miniature of Khan Karkass, in \"Spectral Gobbowl Champion\" mode."};
descriptions["20018"]={cn:"前往地下城门口的兑奖机处兑换酷炫的奖励",en:"Use the machine across from the dungeon to exchange your tokens for fantastic rewards."};
descriptions["20019"]={cn:"通过高阶英雄测试的人将会获得此称号。",en:"A title for those who have passed the tests of the Hardened Hero."};
descriptions["20020"]={cn:"半径，周长和正弦",en:"\"Radius, circumference and sinusoidality\""};
descriptions["20021"]={cn:"所有，完全，统统，你想计算那些球体的一切",en:"\"All, all, all, you\'ll know all about those balls\""};
descriptions["20022"]={cn:"关于绵球球的一切 — 789 版",en:"\"The whole of Gobbowl since its creation\" — 789 Edition"};
descriptions["20023"]={cn:"这东西实在太古老了，只有考古学专家能鉴别它的真伪和效用。",en:"This object is really quite ancient. Only an expert archaosologist can verify its authenticity and usefulness."};
descriptions["20024"]={cn:"一个伟(辣)大(鸡)的袋子，放着你的补偿礼物！",en:"A great big bag to put all your compensation gifts in!"};
descriptions["20025"]={cn:"在阿斯图布传送门旁边的兑换机上使用这些补偿奖章。你能用他们来交换经验卷轴和各种各样的东西。",en:"These tokens can be used in the Compensation Machine near the Astrub Zaap. You can exchange them for experience scrolls and all sorts of things."};
descriptions["20026"]={cn:"我们无法从老师和朋友那学得真正的耐心和忍耐。真正教会我们这些品质的，恰恰是让我们不爽的煞笔们。",en:"We cannot learn real patience and tolerance from gurus or friends. These qualities can be gained only when we come into contact with those who create genuinely unpleasant experiences."};
