descriptions["20033"]={cn:"5000 枚硬币，因爱铸就。",en:"5,000 little Kamas, minted with love."};
descriptions["20035"]={cn:"这张旧纸片上的字迹几乎无法辨认。但你懂得，这笔记正适合菜鸟，对吧？",en:"The writing on this old scrap of paper seem almost illegible. But you do understand that this note is for novices, right?"};
descriptions["20036"]={cn:"据说，一点点这种粉末可以把最粗糙的男人变成挥舞彩虹的仙子。BY自己尝试一下。",en:"It is said that a little of this powder could turn the roughest of men into rainbow-wielding fairies. Don\'t try it yourself."};
descriptions["20037"]={cn:"这颗珍珠很有可能是你要找的！把它完好无损的带回去完成入学任务！",en:"This pearl is probably one of the ones you were sent to find. Bring it back without a scratch to complete your entry!"};
descriptions["20038"]={cn:"致相信光能的人们。",en:"For those who believe in the power of Quadramental Breeze."};
descriptions["20039"]={cn:"高尚指环会掩盖你在植物学学习中收获的...瘀伤。",en:"Nobly hide the bruises on your fingers that you harvested in botanical studies."};
descriptions["20040"]={cn:"让我们保持真诚：披着光能使者的长袍是种痛苦。",en:"Let\'s be sincere: Huppermages\' long robes are a pain to wear."};
descriptions["20041"]={cn:"你的内心感慨万千，这条项链显示了你的社会地位: 一个菜鸟。",en:"Filled with emotion, this amulet shows your position in society: a novice."};
descriptions["20042"]={cn:"有了这件衣服，你再也不用害怕面对前线的敌人了!",en:"With this costume, you won\'t need to fear facing enemies on the frontline any more!"};
descriptions["20043"]={cn:"穿着这件时装你能听见来自千里之外的敌人！",en:"You\'ll be able to hear your enemies from miles off with this costume!"};
descriptions["20044"]={cn:"他们说这件时装能带来好运...现在去找出是为什么！",en:"They say that this costume brings good luck... now go and find out why!"};
descriptions["20046"]={cn:"宠物染料可以于宠物设定介面中更改。此物品已无用处，可以将其分解掉。",en:"Pet colorings can be changed in the pet settings interface. This item is obsolete; you can recycle it."};
descriptions["20047"]={cn:"叮叮作响的珠宝配合这种发饰简直是太完美了。",en:"A great hairstyle to decorate with the most tinkling set of jewels"};
descriptions["20048"]={cn:"带上这个头盔我就知道你想向我扔出一个辣鸡游戏《触控战争》。虽然它可爱又迷人，总是让人忍不住点点点，但是我TM又不是傻鸟！",en:"No one will recognise you under this colorful helmet! Now you\'re a formidable but irresistibly cute soldier, to the point that everyone will want to poke you."};
descriptions["20049"]={cn:"一段神奇的花茎。虽说是消耗品，但是它只会给你带来负面效果。",en:"A stem from a Branchy-Flower. It can be consumed, but will only produce diminished effects."};
descriptions["20051"]={cn:"如果你使用了这个徽章，即使你能打败维伦亚，光能使者们也不会把你当做英雄来看待。",en:"Bearing this emblem, even if you got it on your quest against Vilenya, will not make you a hero in the eyes of the Huppermages."};
descriptions["20052"]={cn:"四系元素在你的身边肆虐。",en:"The four elements rage around you."};
descriptions["20053"]={cn:"一个灵魂却有三种不同的脸孔。三种不同的方式去生，去战，去死。",en:"Three faces but one spirit. Three techniques to live, fight and die."};
descriptions["20054"]={cn:"由於传送门，旅者能在各地自由进出。",en:"Thanks to portals, travelers can always find their way across multiple realities."};
descriptions["20055"]={cn:"最初护符的复制品。它似乎被黑魔法污染了！",en:"This amulet is a copy of the original. It appears to have been altered by dark magic."};
