descriptions["20080"]={cn:"仿佛被施了魔法，你现在被染上了萨弗基亚的颜色。",en:"As if by magic, you now bear the colors of Sufokia."};
descriptions["20081"]={cn:"这可是个非常奇特的绵球坐骑装饰哦！用这个装饰把你的绵球打扮的像个冰坨坨一样吧！",en:"A Gobball War Chief skin to make you look like a frozen Gobball!"};
descriptions["20082"]={cn:"玩家吹响这支笛子能演奏出优美的旋律，可以使青石龙蛋孵化。",en:"This Ocarina lets the player play a sweet melody, in order to make the Lazurite Dofus hatch."};
descriptions["20083"]={cn:"准备好标记你的目标了吗？",en:"Get ready to mark your targets!"};
descriptions["20084"]={cn:"生日快乐乐乐乐乐！沃土生日快乐乐乐乐乐乐乐乐！",en:"Happy Biiirthdaaaaaaaaay! Happy Wakfu Biiirthdaaaaaaaaay!"};
descriptions["20085"]={cn:"像这样摆个光能使者的POSE一定能让你的朋友们印象深刻！",en:"All you need to impress your friends with this Huppermage pose!"};
descriptions["20086"]={cn:"像这样摆个亚伦洛普的POSE一定能让你的朋友们印象深刻！",en:"All you need to impress your friends is this Eliotrope pose!"};
descriptions["20087"]={cn:"各方面都很均匀的包包，但不能将你的头装进去！",en:"A balanced bag, not to be put on your head!"};
descriptions["20088"]={cn:"仔细想想，不氪金你能变的更强吗？",en:"What item will you get in this mystery box?"};
