descriptions["20109"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few grains should suffice."};
descriptions["20110"]={cn:"这种植物纤维既能粘住滋滋，又能毒死它们。所以到了炎热潮湿的地方，尽情的撒一大把吧！",en:"This fiber is both sticky and toxic to Moskitos. Perfect for driving them off in damp and aggressive areas."};
descriptions["20113"]={cn:"汉尼芭人常用的装饰品，这种植物根茎能帮助他们与勇气之神沟通。",en:"Usually used for Kanniball decoctions, these roots help to channel your inner warrior."};
descriptions["20114"]={cn:"这种黏黏的东西用♂的越多越好！",en:"It\'s best to use this sticky substance as soon as possible."};
descriptions["20147"]={cn:"点击两下来把整组古代资源转换成新的符文粉末。古代资源需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["20148"]={cn:"这个黏黏细细的法杖可以救你一命。不要以貌取物好不好！",en:"This sticky, slimy stuff could save your life. Don\'t judge yuck by its cover!"};
descriptions["20149"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Portable, easy to assemble, and ideal for all those unforeseeable moments, from setting off on adventures to picnics with the mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["20150"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Portable, easy to assemble, and ideal for all those unforeseeable moments, from setting off on adventures to picnics with the mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["20151"]={cn:"这对匕首被注入了黑暗魔法，会在晚上攻击它们的主人，因此它们被命名为“西弗勒斯”，一位著名的双料间谍魔法师。这对匕首每隔10年就会变得更加锋利。如果你够聪明的话，就去弄一对用过的匕首，以便观察和研究。",en:"These daggers get their name from the fact they attack their owner at night. They are always sharpened once per decade. It\'s always wise to acquire a used pair of these ancient dark-magic-imbued weapons so their behavior can be observed properly."};
descriptions["20152"]={cn:"这对匕首被注入了黑暗魔法，会在晚上攻击它们的主人，因此它们被命名为“西弗勒斯”，一位著名的双料间谍魔法师。这对匕首每隔10年就会变得更加锋利。如果你够聪明的话，就去弄一对用过的匕首，以便观察和研究。",en:"These daggers get their name from the fact they attack their owner at night. They are always sharpened once per decade. It\'s always wise to acquire a used pair of these ancient dark-magic-imbued weapons so their behavior can be observed properly."};
descriptions["20153"]={cn:"收集100个碎片，合成西弗勒斯匕首。",en:"Collect 100 of these fragments to create a pair of Daggers Sives."};
descriptions["20154"]={cn:"收集100个碎片，合成西弗勒斯匕首。（帐号绑定）",en:"Collect 100 of these fragments to create a pair of Daggers Sives (linked to the account)."};
descriptions["20155"]={cn:"最为老练的汉尼芭人懂得，想要穿越丛林，避免那些触手的骚扰，最好穿上这件胸甲。那些自作聪明的人通常会在丛林之旅中失♂去点什么。",en:"The most senior Kanniballs like to wear this Breastplate, which removes obstacles as they move through the jungle. A few have tripped and lost an arm."};
descriptions["20156"]={cn:"穿上这件披风，你就能够吓走你的敌人并且对着他们逃跑的背影吐口水了。",en:"With this cape, you can gobble up your enemies and spit them back out again."};
descriptions["20157"]={cn:"捕猎者的最佳选择。",en:"Perfect for going off the eaten track."};
descriptions["20158"]={cn:"有一个汉尼芭人高耸入云，但是穿上这个就再也回不去他的村子了。",en:"Originally worn by a Kanniball with his head in the clouds, we now know why he never returned to the village."};
descriptions["20159"]={cn:"如果这个胸甲不能吸引异性的话，至少它漂亮的颜色能让它成为一个很好的捕蝇器。",en:"This won\'t attract your crush but the vibrant colors of this breastplate can act as a fly catcher."};
descriptions["20160"]={cn:"戴上这个戒指你就会不由自主的想吃东西，并且吃的相当快。",en:"Wearers of this ring often have an uncontrollable urge to eat a lot and very quickly."};
descriptions["20161"]={cn:"嘘，戴上这腰带你就是政府的人了。",en:"I Am Legend! And you?"};
descriptions["20162"]={cn:"这种时髦软帽的经典款是由纯植物材料制造的。当然啦，也有一些暴发户和皮条客更喜欢金属版的。",en:"Who said doggies are our best friends? You must not have known about this hat, which will never let you down. The opposite, however, is not so certain."};
descriptions["20163"]={cn:"这种肩甲需要浸泡在酒精中，所以戴上它的人可能会有点晕乎乎的，不过也更……快乐？",en:"These epaulettes have been soaked in plant extract, which causes the wearer to become dazed but merry."};
descriptions["20164"]={cn:"这款项链的原名叫做“安琪帕罗格的珍贵坠饰”，太绕口了是不是？所以给它改名啦！",en:"This necklace was renamed. \"Archipelago Necklet\" was considered too much of a mouthful."};
descriptions["20165"]={cn:"这就是传说中的莱斯披风！",en:"It\'s a total Cape Rice!"};
descriptions["20166"]={cn:"我跟你讲，这个胸甲一年包换！而且你不觉得感恩节的时候，它看上去很美味吗？",en:"This armor offers very good protection for at least one year. It looks particularly beautiful in the summer too."};
descriptions["20167"]={cn:"这种靴子曾被禁止使用过。因为它的气味实在是让人绝望，甚至会导致自杀倾向——尤其是在地铁公交等场所。",en:"These espadrilles used to be banned. The fragrance given off by the plants can cause feelings of hopelessness and self-destructive tendencies."};
descriptions["20168"]={cn:"这顶时髦的帽子深受富人们的喜爱。它由一种月亮岛特有的植物纤维所制成。",en:"A stylish hat usually favored by the wealthy. It is made from a specific type of plant fiber found only on Moon Island."};
descriptions["20169"]={cn:"曾经拥有这个手环的水手已消失在海洋中那片神秘海域，它一定是在这儿被冲上了月亮岛。即便如此，直到现在那名水手依旧杳无音讯。",en:"This bracelet washed up on Moon Island, along with some Possessed Epaulettes. It can now be worn on your finger."};
descriptions["20170"]={cn:"当地最美味的蘑菇汤！没有比它更好的了——因为只有这一种。",en:"The best local mushroom soup bar none! In fact, it\'s the only one!"};
descriptions["20171"]={cn:"这个制甲师配方，让你学会制作“火鸡胸”",en:"This blueprint will teach you the recipe for the item \"Bawk Bak\" for the Armorer profession."};
descriptions["20172"]={cn:"这个皮匠配方，让你学会制作“凤爪登山靴”",en:"This blueprint will teach you the recipe for the item \"Equal Espadrilles\" for the Leather Dealer profession."};
descriptions["20173"]={cn:"这张图纸记载着裁缝配方“鸡冠帽”",en:"This blueprint will teach you the recipe for the item \"Conkman\" for the Tailor profession."};
descriptions["20174"]={cn:"这张图纸记载着裁缝配方“莱斯披风”",en:"This blueprint will teach you the recipe for the item \"Cape Rice\" for the Tailor profession."};
descriptions["20175"]={cn:"这个珠宝师配方，让你学会制作“百慕项链”",en:"This blueprint will teach you the recipe for the item \"Possessed Bracelet\" for the Jeweler profession."};
descriptions["20176"]={cn:"一块固态水银。小心轻放，远离热源。",en:"A block of solid Mercury. Handle with care and keep away from heat sources."};
descriptions["20177"]={cn:"据说镀铬的水银能愈合伤口。但也许这还有别的用途？",en:"It is said that Chrome-Plated Mercury heals wounds. But maybe it\'s used for something else?"};
descriptions["20178"]={cn:"如果你对于邪恶的海狼鱼毫无畏惧，那就咬它一口。小心点，它即便快死了也很凶猛。",en:"If you\'re not afraid of the big, bad sea Boowolf, why don\'t you try to take a bite out of it? Careful though, apparently it\'s just as tough dead as it is alive."};
descriptions["20179"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["20180"]={cn:"在肆月种下，以后可以收获一片淡雅的粉色。",en:"Try planting this cutting in Aperirel for a beautiful shade of pink."};
descriptions["20181"]={cn:"坚硬、强韧，充满了樱桃的香气。",en:"This wood is strong, healthy, and imbued with the delicious fragrance of cherries."};
descriptions["20182"]={cn:"在樱花上浇些开水，想想未来；就在下一秒。别忘了，凉茶入杯，会改变其稳定世界的平衡。",en:"Pour some boiling water over the Sakura, think about the future; it\'s only the next second. Don\'t forget that pouring the tea into the mug while it\'s still cold changes the equilibrium of their stable worlds."};
descriptions["20183"]={cn:"在陆地上播种一个或两个孢子，一大批死帽蕈就可能覆盖整个世界！",en:"Scatter a spore or two on the ground, and an army of Death Caps could rise unheeded to take over the world!"};
descriptions["20184"]={cn:"经过妥善的加工，这种菌菇的毒性会消失，并且让人赞不绝口。",en:"When prepared properly, this mushroom is less death and more \"dddarn, that\'s good!\""};
descriptions["20185"]={cn:"在烹调这只蘑菇之前，记得拔光所有的毛。",en:"Before cooking this mushroom, don\'t forget to pluck out all of its hairs."};
descriptions["20186"]={cn:"南瓜种子是很可怕的！只吃几颗就能让你的头肿得和南瓜一样大！",en:"Pumpkin Seeds are scary! Just eat a few and your head will swell to the size of the pumpkin they came from!"};
descriptions["20187"]={cn:"南瓜是南瓜家族里一种可以食用的植物，通常做成南瓜汤或者南瓜泥。当然你也可以戴在头上...",en:"The Pumpkin is an edible plant of the family Cucurbitaceae, which can be eaten as a soup or mash. You can also put it on your head..."};
descriptions["20188"]={cn:"双击将古代资源转换为新的资源,古代资源请尽快使用，将在未来某个版本删除",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["20191"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few grains should suffice."};
descriptions["20192"]={cn:"十分的坚硬，刚刚从一只尼罗鳄的背上挖下来的。这种行为是不是只有傻子才会这么做？",en:"Hard and rigid, freshly harvested from a Crocodyl\'s back. Surely only a fool would try that?"};
descriptions["20193"]={cn:"鳄鱼皮的质量十分值得质疑，可能并没有那么值钱。",en:"Crocodyl Leather of very dubious quality. It\'s probably not worth very much."};
descriptions["20194"]={cn:"弄丢了不要紧，另一个会出现在你发现它的相同位置的。",en:"If you lose this one, you might find another will grow in its place."};
descriptions["20195"]={cn:"点击两下来把整组古代资源转换成新的符文粉末。古代资源需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["20196"]={cn:"一面带着骷髅头标志的旗子，曾经盖在尼罗王的后背。",en:"A black flag bearing a skull and crossbones, which once covered the Nyl King\'s back."};
descriptions["20197"]={cn:"小型绵球球比赛胜利后从鳄爵丹迪那获得的。",en:"The hat won from Crocodyl Dandy after a little Gobball race."};
descriptions["20198"]={cn:"他们悄悄告诉你，这个卡牌的使用者维斯特曾经拥有过一段凄美的爱情故事。\"哦！坎耶，坎耶 为什么你偏偏是坎耶·维斯特呢？否认你的父亲，抛弃你的姓名吧；也许你不愿意这样做，那么只要你宣誓做我的爱人，我也不愿再姓凯普莱特了。\"所以，也没什么大不了的。",en:"They say that these cards once had luscious black locks and were mad about another card player, the Vwest, whispering sweet nothings like... \"Oh Kannye! Kannye! Wherefore art thou, Kannye? Deny thy father and refuse thy name; or if thou wilt not, be but sworn my love, and I\'ll no longer be a Capulet!\" So nothing too serious."};
descriptions["20199"]={cn:"一定要握紧了，不然从你手中滑出掉到地上，那可就不好办了，你懂的...",en:"Make sure to hold it very tightly, or it will slip out of your hands."};
descriptions["20200"]={cn:"一把轻便的魔杖，帮助你在精确打击中得心应手。",en:"A lightweight and easy-to-handle wand that makes precision work a breeze."};
descriptions["20201"]={cn:"纯金打造，二万一克。红宝石镶嵌，权力之象征。",en:"A magnificent crocodyl head molded in gold with ruby eyes."};
descriptions["20202"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with the mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["20203"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with the mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["20204"]={cn:"这个项链不会带给你任何的好运，它只是骨头和羽毛的混合装饰品，挺好看的哈？",en:"This charm won\'t bring you luck, it\'s just a piece of string with a feather and a bone. It\'s quite nice though."};
descriptions["20205"]={cn:"一件由尼罗鳄皮做的华丽披风。你的套装是不是就差这件了啊？",en:"A beautiful and extravagant cloak made from Crocodyl skin. Just what you need to complete your set!"};
descriptions["20206"]={cn:"尼罗鳄的鳞片制作的漂亮靴子，适合在沙滩散步！",en:"Beautiful boots made from Crocodyl scales. Perfect for the beach!"};
descriptions["20207"]={cn:"鳄鱼皮腰带外加骷髅扣，冒险者必备的流行款式。",en:"A Crocodyl leather belt with a nice skull buckle. Essential fashion for adventurers."};
descriptions["20208"]={cn:"这华丽头饰之下藏着一颗鳄鱼的头骨，那是一只有名的鳄鱼，他曾流下了真正的眼泪。我们倾向于认为，头颅与身躯分离之际，鳄鱼将会流下它的眼泪。",en:"This magnificent headgear bears the skull of a famous Crocodyl who was said to cry real Crocodyl tears. We\'re tempted to believe that said tears were shed as its head was about to be removed from its body."};
descriptions["20209"]={cn:"这个戒指是用鳄鱼牙齿打磨成的，一颗像剃刀般锋利的鳄鱼牙。",en:"A razor sharp Crocodyl tooth set into a ring."};
descriptions["20210"]={cn:"我知道你一直想尝试“死亡翻滚”那个高难度动作，现在有了这个护甲的保护，你可以试试了。不过这东西不一定管用，毕竟你又不是尼罗鳄！",en:"With this armor you can finally attempt that \"death roll\" move you\'ve often dreamed about.  Although it probably won\'t work, because you\'re not a Crocodyl."};
descriptions["20211"]={cn:"小巧漂亮的鳄鱼皮靴。高端时尚！",en:"A small pair of smart, scaly Crocodyl-skin boots. High fashion!"};
descriptions["20212"]={cn:"少年，你想成为新世界的卡密吗？穿上它，你的愿望就能满足。",en:"Aggressive epaulettes to satisfy your kamikaze cravings."};
descriptions["20213"]={cn:"尼罗鳄船上的海盗旗被扯下来做成了披肩。",en:"A cape made from the pirate flag from the Nyl boat."};
descriptions["20214"]={cn:"华丽的木雕皇冠，镶嵌着尼罗王的宝石。",en:"An ornate carved wooden crown, set with jewels of the Nyl."};
descriptions["20215"]={cn:"锐利坚硬，近战必备。",en:"Sharp and strong, ideal for improving your melee fighting."};
descriptions["20216"]={cn:"点缀着可爱的金色宝石，小到潜水大至打架，这腰带都是绝佳装备。",en:"Embellished with a lovely golden gem, this belt is ideal for jumping into the fray."};
descriptions["20217"]={cn:"这件胸甲是由鳄鱼鳞片制成的。",en:"A heavy breastplate made of Crocodyl scales"};
descriptions["20218"]={cn:"由牙齿和鳞片制成，这些靴子当然可以被归类为护具。",en:"Made of teeth and scales, these boots can certainly be classed as protective gear."};
descriptions["20219"]={cn:"它不会增加你的咬合力，但会增加你的自愈能力。",en:"It won\'t improve your bite, but it will increase your healing powers."};
descriptions["20220"]={cn:"别被这个头盔的凶恶外表吓到了，这种设计只是用来保证你的私人空间的，而不是方便对敌人发起冲锋的。看到这个可怕的大角，你的敌人肯定不敢接近你的。",en:"Don\'t be fooled by the enormous horn, this helmet is made to preserve your personal space, not for charging. Opponents won\'t dare to come near you and your impressive horn."};
descriptions["20221"]={cn:"这个护身符是用凶猛野兽的牙齿制成的。",en:"A monstrous tooth mounted on an Amulet."};
descriptions["20222"]={cn:"这套卡牌挺好的，就是有点扎手。",en:"Cards with a little bite!"};
descriptions["20223"]={cn:"强大的指针武器，远程职业的完美选择。",en:"A formidable Hand, ideal for distance attacks."};
descriptions["20224"]={cn:"阿卡菲儿是一位漂亮的安妮丽莎菇凉，她喜欢械勒人的魔法。但失败的魔法实验让她丢失了两把心爱的猴哥棒。有了这个她终于不用再次辛苦的挖矿来做第三把猴哥棒了。",en:"Its hard-looking heart is as mighty as the power it wields. Handle with the utmost care."};
descriptions["20225"]={cn:"良心商家出品：厚度感人的胸甲，在战斗中给你更感人的保护。",en:"An armor of impressive thickness that provides incredible protection during a fight."};
descriptions["20226"]={cn:"你一定听说过蝙蝠披风，那我们给你一件鳄鱼披风！固然是少了点小配件，但还是很威风的。",en:"You\'ve heard of the Batcape, we give you the Crococape! A few less gadgets admittedly, but still very impressive."};
descriptions["20227"]={cn:"绷带混着鳄鱼牙齿，结实的尖牙绑腿。",en:"Solid leggings bristling with crocodyl teeth."};
descriptions["20228"]={cn:"一枚迷人的鳄鱼蛋……听说这个蛋具有神奇的功效，能够医死人肉白骨。",en:"Here\'s an intriguing Crocodyl egg... They say that it has astonishing properties and can heal serious injuries."};
descriptions["20229"]={cn:"利用这个腰带和桅杆上的滑轮可以有效的避免涨潮时湿身——老司机们都懂得。",en:"A mast pulley, cleverly tied to make a belt. Will particularly appeal to sailors."};
descriptions["20230"]={cn:"这个武器大师配方，让你学会制作“毒牙卡牌”",en:"This blueprint will teach you the recipe for the \"Fanged Cards\" item for the Weapons Master profession."};
descriptions["20231"]={cn:"这个武器大师配方，让你学会制作“狡猾指针”",en:"This blueprint will teach you the recipe for the \"Slippyneedle\" item for the Weapons Master profession."};
descriptions["20232"]={cn:"这个武器大师配方，让你学会制作“雷克赛内特指针”",en:"This blueprint will teach you the recipe for the \"The Recssenette\" item for the Weapons Master profession."};
descriptions["20233"]={cn:"这张图纸记载着制甲师配方 \"尼罗王胸甲\"",en:"This blueprint will teach you the recipe for the item \"Nyl Breastplate\" for the Armorer profession."};
descriptions["20234"]={cn:"这张图纸记载着裁缝配方 \"鳄鱼披风\"",en:"This blueprint will teach you the recipe for the item \"Crococape\" for the Tailor profession."};
descriptions["20235"]={cn:"这张图纸记载着皮匠配方 \"尖牙绑腿\"",en:"This blueprint will teach you the recipe for the item \"Pointy Leggings\" for the Leather Dealer profession."};
descriptions["20236"]={cn:"这张图纸记载着珠宝师配方 \"萨满神蛋\"",en:"This blueprint will teach you the recipe for the item \"Shamanic Egg\" for the Jeweler profession."};
descriptions["20237"]={cn:"这张图纸记载着皮匠配方 \"高潮腰带\"",en:"This blueprint will teach you the recipe for the item \"The High Hoist\" for the Leather Dealer profession."};
descriptions["20238"]={cn:"这东西实在太古老了，只有考古学专家能鉴别它的真伪和效用。",en:"This object is really quite ancient. Only an expert archaosologist can verify its authenticity and usefulness."};
descriptions["20239"]={cn:"完成精英英雄测试的称号奖励！",en:"A title for those who have passed the tests of the Tough Hero."};
descriptions["20240"]={cn:"前往地下城门口的兑奖机处兑换酷炫的奖励。",en:"Use the machine across from the dungeon to exchange your tokens for fantastic rewards."};
descriptions["20241"]={cn:"值得加入你私人收藏的奖杯。",en:"A nice trophy for your personal collection."};
descriptions["20246"]={cn:"这件绒毛丰厚的披风能够让你在冬天里既暖和又拉风！",en:"This heavy fur cape will keep you nice and warm in winter!"};
descriptions["20247"]={cn:"这可是你费了九哞二虎之力才搞到的，你就别抱怨款式了！",en:"You\'ve moved heaven and earth to get them, so don\'t complain now!"};
descriptions["20248"]={cn:"可以放在书架上当漂亮的镇纸。",en:"These would make for a lovely book weight on your shelf."};
descriptions["20249"]={cn:"一块木雕的小坠饰，上面有着描绘月神的雕刻。",en:"A small pendant of carved wood, sculpted to depict Moon."};
descriptions["20250"]={cn:"就没人跟你说过你长得像一只小猴子么？！",en:"Hasn\'t anyone told you you look just like a little monkey?!"};
descriptions["20251"]={cn:"这件大号猴毛腰带是提升你男子气概的完美道具。",en:"The big monkey-fur belt is perfect for increasing your virility."};
descriptions["20252"]={cn:"你没法教一只老猴子怎么扮鬼脸。那有什么关系呢？没什么关系...",en:"You can\'t teach an old monkey how to pull faces. What\'s that got to do with it? Nothing whatsoever..."};
descriptions["20253"]={cn:"这件胸甲能让你穿的像个金刚一样，对吧。",en:"A breastplate that\'s perfect for dressing up as King Kong, right?"};
descriptions["20254"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with the mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["20255"]={cn:"一胸当关，万夫莫开。",en:"Dive into a fight chest-first to crush your enemies."};
descriptions["20256"]={cn:"戴着这顶前卫锐利的头盔蔑视敌人的穿衣品味吧。",en:"Look down on your opponents thanks to this sharp headgear."};
descriptions["20257"]={cn:"只要你脑袋还没搬家，这件披风就不会脱落。",en:"It won\'t fall off, so long as you still have a neck to hold it in place."};
descriptions["20258"]={cn:"萃取自然之力，赋予你的箭矢杀手本能。",en:"Give your arrows a murderous instinct, drawn from the forces of nature."};
descriptions["20259"]={cn:"前往地下城门口的兑奖机处兑换酷炫的奖励。",en:"Use the machine across from the dungeon to exchange your tokens for fantastic rewards."};
descriptions["20260"]={cn:"小心保管：这些爪子依然想挠死你。",en:"Handle with caution: these claws still want to kill you."};
descriptions["20261"]={cn:"据说还没有人能从活豆芙身上拔下这么一根毛。不过可能是因为没人试过...",en:"It\'s said that no one has ever managed to pluck one of these feathers from a living Tofu. Then again, it\'s unlikely anyone\'s tried..."};
descriptions["20262"]={cn:"这只利喙什么都啄 - 连你的手指也不会放过。",en:"This beak can peck at anything - even your fingers."};
descriptions["20263"]={cn:"把爪子、羽毛、喙都去掉之后，这只豆芙看上去远没那么危险了。",en:"Once you get rid of its claws, feathers and beak, this Tofu looks far less dangerous!"};
descriptions["20265"]={cn:"为了给你呈上这盘菜，多少猎人殒命途中。",en:"Many hunters died bringing you this dish."};
descriptions["20266"]={cn:"穿上这件火辣辣的时装，你就能上天辣！",en:"You\'ll be all fired up with this hot costume."};
descriptions["20267"]={cn:"有了复苏之春时装，你走在哪里，哪里就是春天！",en:"An outfit to put spring in your step!"};
descriptions["20268"]={cn:"小心点，这身行头很容易激怒某些人。",en:"Be careful, it\'s easy to ruffle a few feathers with this outfit."};
descriptions["20269"]={cn:"承认吧，你总是会被愚弄。因此这件时装跟你实在是太搭了！",en:"Admit it, you\'re bound to be fooled this Aperirel, so you might as well wear the costume."};
descriptions["20270"]={cn:"无论在微博还是在推特，这件时装的点赞数都突破了天际。",en:"Fantastic outfit for twick or tweeting."};
descriptions["20271"]={cn:"外行人玩不转这个，高端玩家专用。",en:"Not for the average layperson, this makes you a high-end egg beater."};
descriptions["20272"]={cn:"戴上这对翅膀并不会让你看起来像个天使，别人还没那么傻！但是至少，会让你看上去很“经典”。",en:"These wings won\'t be able to fool people into thinking you\'re an angel. But they will make you look very classy."};
descriptions["20273"]={cn:"让我萌去治愈世界吧！",en:"Let\'s go and heal the world!"};
descriptions["20274"]={cn:"他 看 起 来 真 可 爱！",en:"Look how cute he is!"};
descriptions["20276"]={cn:"数十年前，简·赫敏·施配克的远征队发现了这里。数十年后，达尔斯·查尔文为此地引进了这一珍稀的物种。 他的丰功伟业实际上是窃取了施配克的成就，但是并没有其他人知道……",en:"This previously rare variety was brought back by Darles Charwin, after an expedition following in the footsteps of Jan Honning Speck, several decades ago. He stole this find hands down, a perfectly appropriate expression for poor Speck, who now has but one..."};
descriptions["20277"]={cn:"你以前见过喜欢在手上戴戒指的猴子么？",en:"Have you found a monkey who\'d like a ring on their finger?"};
descriptions["20278"]={cn:"这件护肩来自一个古老的国度，据说它曾经的主人是一个精通战争艺术和秘法的猴子国王。",en:"These epaulettes come from an ancient kingdom, and it\'s said they belonged to a Monkey King, an expert in martial arts and master of secret bō techniques."};
descriptions["20279"]={cn:"以月之锤为原型打造，这件武器蕴含着惊人的魔法力量。",en:"Following the example of the Moon Hammer, this weapon contains a surprising, magical power."};
descriptions["20280"]={cn:"从月神身上取下的一丛毛发。",en:"A clump of hair taken from Sham Moon."};
descriptions["20281"]={cn:"一件专精于单体伤害的徽章。",en:"An insignia specializing in Single Target Mastery."};
descriptions["20282"]={cn:"历尽艰险的你赢得的奖励。你可以用这枚奖章兑换装备。",en:"You can trade in this hard-won token for pieces of equipment."};
