descriptions["20293"]={cn:"这顶头盔曾属于一名专业的飞行员，他在飞过月亮岛上空时失踪。",en:"This helmet belonged to an Imp pilot who disappeared while flying over Moon Island."};
descriptions["20294"]={cn:"传奇大师打造的传奇斗篷。",en:"An epic cloak belonging to an epic Cra."};
descriptions["20295"]={cn:"一条蓝绳子上简单的挂着一个奇怪的小娃娃，然而这护符特别实用。",en:"A strange little doll, hanging from a blue cord. It\'s very effective, nonetheless."};
