descriptions["20356"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["20357"]={cn:"总是有花汁时不时的从这件武器上滴落，搞的满手黏黏答答的。",en:"Sap constantly trickles out of this weapon, which makes it sticky from end to end."};
descriptions["20358"]={cn:"击败叛逆植物的必备武器。",en:"An essential weapon for fighting off rebellious plants."};
descriptions["20359"]={cn:"像这样摆个凯拉的POSE一定能让你的朋友们印象深刻！",en:"Impress your friends with this Cra pose!"};
descriptions["20360"]={cn:"一件值得加入私人收藏的战利品。",en:"A nice trophy for your personal collection."};
descriptions["20361"]={cn:"袋子上镶着四块完美的翡翠石...能用来做什么呢？",en:"A pouch with four emeralds of great purity... What could they be used for?"};
descriptions["20362"]={cn:"一件专精于范围伤害的徽章。",en:"An insignia specializing in Area Mastery."};
descriptions["20363"]={cn:"一件专精于近战伤害的徽章。",en:"An insignia specializing in melee mastery."};
descriptions["20364"]={cn:"一件专精于远程伤害的徽章。",en:"An insignia specializing in Distance Mastery."};
descriptions["20365"]={cn:"一件通用的大师徽章。",en:"A master key insignia, useful to all."};
descriptions["20366"]={cn:"这不是著名的亚伦立方吗？至少是个复制品...",en:"Isn\'t this the famous Eliocube? Or a replica, at least..."};
descriptions["20367"]={cn:"一个拥有惊人能力的盾牌，并不仅仅指它的防卫能力，而是指它能够扩大持有者视野的能力。也许秘密藏在这双翡翠眼睛里...",en:"A shield of surprising efficiency, not due to its resistance, but its ability to improve its bearer\'s vision. Maybe it has something to do with the emerald eyes..."};
descriptions["20368"]={cn:"一件专精于狂暴伤害的徽章。",en:"An insignia specializing in Berserk Mastery."};
descriptions["20369"]={cn:"一件专精于背刺伤害的徽章。",en:"An insignia specializing in Rear Mastery."};
descriptions["20370"]={cn:"据说，奥铎迈的门徒穿着这双鞋周游十二世界，寻找宝藏和生物...",en:"It is said that Otomai\'s pilgrims wore these shoes to travel the World of Twelve in search of treasures and creatures..."};
descriptions["20371"]={cn:"头几次的试炼总是会给奥铎迈的新门徒带来丰富的收获。这就是为什么他们会用这身盔甲来准备面对生活中的任何挑战。",en:"The first few trials always give colorful results for Otomai\'s initiates. That\'s why they use this armor to be ready for whatever life throws at them."};
descriptions["20372"]={cn:"在造访新地域之前，奥铎迈的斥候会被派去执行侦察任务，装备着这副护腿。",en:"Before visiting new lands, Otomai\'s Scouts are sent on reconnaissance missions, equipped with these very greaves."};
descriptions["20373"]={cn:"奥铎迈的斥候给了你一顶简单但结实的头盔。明智地使用它！",en:"Otomai\'s Scouts have given you a simple, but sturdy helmet. Use it wisely!"};
descriptions["20374"]={cn:"奥铎迈的斥候在执行侦察任务时通过他们的斗篷相互识别。",en:"Otomai\'s Scouts recognize one another by their cloaks when they\'re out on reconnaissance missions."};
descriptions["20375"]={cn:"这张图纸记载着制甲师配方  \"猴王肩甲\"",en:"This blueprint will teach you the recipe for the relic \"Monkey King Epaulettes\" for the Armorer profession."};
descriptions["20376"]={cn:"这些毁灭能量制作而成的靴子在它们为你开路之前已经磨损了相当长一段时间……",en:"These boots made from Stasis have been worn for quite some time before making their way to you..."};
descriptions["20377"]={cn:"尽管对力量的感觉使你带上这个护符，你还是感到一种无法抑制的冲动，它使你渴望着像葛优一样瘫坐不起。",en:"Despite the feeling of power you get from wearing this amulet, you feel an irrepressible urge to sit down and never get up again."};
descriptions["20378"]={cn:"戴着这个戒指越长时间，你手指的数目也会……",en:"The longer you wear this ring, the number your finger will get..."};
descriptions["20379"]={cn:"每披一次这件披风，它都好像变得更重了。",en:"This cloak seems to get heavier every time you put it on."};
descriptions["20380"]={cn:"别长时间戴着这顶被污染的帽子。它可能会使你头疼，也可能让你长出第三只耳朵……",en:"Don\'t wear this Stasified hat for too long. It might give you a nasty headache, or you may grow a third ear..."};
descriptions["20381"]={cn:"如果你系着这条腰带太久，你可能会发现你的消化系统变得有点......倒退。",en:"If you wear this belt for too long, you may find your digestive system gets a little... backed up."};
descriptions["20382"]={cn:"乍一看是个普通的夸夸肩甲，实际上，是个毁灭能量和肩甲的奇特组合。",en:"What at first glance looks to be a simple Iop shoulderpad is, in fact, a strange mix of Stasis and flesh."};
descriptions["20383"]={cn:"我们不建议你穿着着这身毁灭水晶太长时间。特别是你还喜欢呼吸的话。",en:"We don\'t recommend you wear this Stasis Crystal vice for too long. Especially not if you like breathing."};
descriptions["20384"]={cn:"有人觉得这戒指套着你，而不是你戴着它。",en:"Some people think this rings wears you, not the other way around."};
descriptions["20385"]={cn:"这是少数还没有被毁灭力所污染的因卡纳姆物品之一。",en:"This is one of the few Incarnam items that has not been contaminated by Stasis."};
descriptions["20388"]={cn:"这药水是由奥铎曼创造的，据说能治愈被毁灭能量污染的植物。现在，你所要做的就是证明这一点……",en:"This concoction, created by the legendary alchemist Otomai, is said to be able to cure plants contaminated by Stasis. Now all you have to do is prove it..."};
descriptions["20389"]={cn:"这特别的罗盘能帮你找出沙雕在哪里。",en:"This special compass will help you find where the Sändskates come from."};
descriptions["20390"]={cn:"这把钥匙能打开通往手工沙雕世界的大门。\n使你可以进入海洋宫殿。",en:"A key which will open the door to a an artisanal and skätey world.\nUnlocks the entrance to the Märine Pälace dungeon."};
descriptions["20391"]={cn:"前往哥纳特之神旁边的兑奖机处用奖章兑换酷炫的奖励。",en:"Exchange your token for some nice rewards at the machine near Gnat, the Meridia."};
descriptions["20392"]={cn:"前往哥纳特之神旁边的兑奖机处用珍珠兑换酷炫的奖励。",en:"Exchange your pearl for some nice rewards at the machine near Gnat, the Meridia."};
descriptions["20393"]={cn:"提供至上的保护、卓越的远见和杀手的冷酷。",en:"The ultimate protection, giving you great vision and a killer look."};
descriptions["20394"]={cn:"头顶戴着的这只时尚的章鱼会不停地按摩你的头皮。喱维萨沙滩休闲必备！",en:"Capillary massages are guaranteed with this fashionable octopus on your head. You\'ll mix the relaxation and must-have of the beaches of Bilbiza."};
descriptions["20395"]={cn:"如果你是海底穴居动物的化身，这件披风能助你轻松穿越海底沙地和隧道，当然还有水族馆。",en:"If you have the soul of a burrower, this cape will make moving around in sandy and aquatic tunnels and galleries much easier."};
descriptions["20396"]={cn:"有了这双脚蹼，至少到目前为止都不会沉下去了！轻而易举，不是吗！",en:"Wearing these flippers, you\'ll never have sunken so far, so easily. It\'s a piece of cake, I tell you!"};
descriptions["20397"]={cn:"这些小海胆舒服的窝在你肩膀上，用突刺攻击胆敢靠近的任何敌人。",en:"These little urchins are cozy on your shoulders, and especially prickly for any enemy who dare approach them."};
descriptions["20398"]={cn:"如果你想在沙滩上滑冰，这款鸭子游泳圈是夏日时尚的必备单品。",en:"This Duck Swim Ring is THE touch of summer fashion, and a must-have if you want to skäte on the beach."};
descriptions["20399"]={cn:"你会无意犯罪吗？ 这枚戒指会增加你看不起对手时压倒对手的机会。",en:"Could you commit a sudden crime? This ring increases the chances of you overwhelming your opponent while looking down on them."};
descriptions["20400"]={cn:"如果你迷路了，你所要做的就是把耳朵贴在贝壳上，倾听它。",en:"If you\'re lost, all you have to do is put your ear to this shell and listen to it."};
descriptions["20401"]={cn:"这类棘皮动物的结构特征在于它们的真皮内骨骼，是由每一个分离的晶体不断积累钙盐形成的，最后融合成星状。嗨！海星！",en:"This echinodermic fabric is characterized by a dermal endoskeleton, formed of individual crystals, forming fused spicules. Hey! A starfish!"};
descriptions["20402"]={cn:"这权杖可作很多事情。你的想像力就是你的“触手”。",en:"Freshly cut from a baby Koutoulou, this staff can be used for many things. It\'s up to you to \"tentacle\" your imagination."};
descriptions["20403"]={cn:"“今天，明天，直到世界末日：史盖特沙漠中史盖特的绿洲！”C.Drinkaire",en:"\"Today, tomorrow, until the end of days: an oasis for the Skäter in a desert of skätes!\" C. Drinkaire"};
descriptions["20404"]={cn:"根据一个尚无定论的传说，这把剑被生活在海边的贝拉当作梳子用。",en:"According to an inconclusive legend, this sword was used as a comb by Bellaphones living near the sea."};
descriptions["20405"]={cn:"非常实用的匕首，可以撬开所有种类的贝壳和战舰。",en:"A practical knife for opening all kinds of shells and battleships."};
descriptions["20406"]={cn:"抓住它，它可能会从你的手中滑出去。",en:"Hold onto it tightly, it could slip out of your hands!"};
descriptions["20407"]={cn:"一顶完全防紫外线的沙滩帽！",en:"A sandy hat with complete UV protection!"};
descriptions["20408"]={cn:"值得加入你私人收藏的奖杯。",en:"A nice trophy for your personal collection."};
descriptions["20409"]={cn:"值得加入你私人收藏的奖杯。",en:"A nice trophy for your personal collection."};
descriptions["20410"]={cn:"一个小瓶子，历经夹着沙子的海水的冲刷，里面的信息显然已经不复存在了。",en:"A little bottle, damaged by the sea and sand, with an apparently unreadable message inside."};
descriptions["20411"]={cn:"一小堆细沙，埋藏着夏天的小秘密。",en:"A small pile of fine sänd, just to bring back some summer memories."};
descriptions["20412"]={cn:"值得加入你私人收藏的小船儿。",en:"A nice ship for your personal collection."};
descriptions["20413"]={cn:"这细砂深受贝壳圣徒奈特的珍视。",en:"This fine sänd is highly prized by Gnat, the Meridia."};
descriptions["20414"]={cn:"这些沙子 - 比白色更黑 - 受每日之神格奈特的高度重视。",en:"This Sänd - which is blacker than white - is highly prized by Gnat, the Meridia."};
descriptions["20415"]={cn:"这个配方会教你学会制作迷你酥饼。",en:"This scroll will teach you the recipe for Little Shortbread Biscuits."};
descriptions["20416"]={cn:"口感一点也不像面包，更像是沙子...",en:"This biscuits taste nothing like bread, more like sand..."};
descriptions["20417"]={cn:"鲍弗森的复制品，杰克·利利·史壮的伙伴。",en:"A certified copy of Boufson, Jacky Lilye Tstrong\'s companion."};
descriptions["20418"]={cn:"好心的老杰克·利利·史壮随意制作的书架。",en:"A haphazardly-made bookcase, by the good old Jacky Lilye Tstrong."};
descriptions["20419"]={cn:"作为新人的第一件外装！\达到15级可以穿上这件外装。",en:"Your first outfit as a young Incarnate!\nReach level 15 to be able to equip this costume."};
descriptions["20423"]={cn:"这页看起来像某本日志的第 1 项。半消化的它看起来非常破旧。\n以下是你看的懂的部分：\n\"第 1 项\n我：「我想这艘船的主人 - 尼罗。我, 宝石...\"",en:"This page looks like the first entry of a logbook. It looks very old and half-digested. This is what you manage to decipher:\n\"ENTRY 1\nMy word! I seem to be the owner of a boat - the Nyl. Me, Gem...\""};
descriptions["20424"]={cn:"这页看起来像某本日志的第 12 项。半消化的它看起来非常破旧。\n以下是你看的懂的部分：\n\"第 12 项\n真是场灾难! 我想这都建立在我的...\"",en:"This page looks like entry 12 of a logbook. It looks very old and half-digested. This is what you manage to decipher:\n\"ENTRY 12\nWhat a catastrophe! And I thought that having my establishment on...\""};
descriptions["20425"]={cn:"这页看起来像某本日志的第 14 项。半消化的它看起来非常破旧。\n以下是你看的懂的部分：\n\"第 14 项\n\"该说什么呢...我的计划都执行的非常完美, 而且完全失败。我会解释...\"",en:"This page looks like entry 14 of a logbook. It looks very old and half-digested. This is what you manage to decipher:\n\"ENTRY 14\nWhat to say... My plan both worked perfectly, and failed miserably. I\'ll explain...\""};
descriptions["20426"]={cn:"这页看起来像某本日志的第 15 项。半消化的它看起来非常破旧。\n以下是你看的懂的部分：\n\"第 15 项\n藉由打给我几个固定的客户, 我得到了两份合同, 这将非常...\"",en:"This page looks like entry 15 of a logbook. It looks very old and half-digested. This is what you manage to decipher:\n\"ENTRY 15\nBy playing a couple of my regular clients, I was able to get a couple of contracts, which would be very...\""};
descriptions["20427"]={cn:"这页看起来像某本日志的第 21 项。半消化的它看起来非常破旧。\n以下是你看的懂的部分：\n\"第 21 项\n经过几个月隐藏\"谨慎\"的交通工具在官方的交通工具下, 我终于找到了...\"",en:"This page looks like entry 21 of a logbook. It looks very old and half-digested. This is what you manage to decipher:\n\"ENTRY 21\nAfter several months of hiding \"discreet\" transportations under cover of official transportations, I\'ve finally found...\""};
descriptions["20428"]={cn:"这页看起来像某本日志的第 25 项。半消化的它看起来非常破旧。\n以下是你看的懂的部分：\n\"第 25 项\n我有一个好点子。\n我一个晚上在竞技场赚到的卡玛比...一星期还多...\"",en:"This page looks like entry 25 of a logbook. It looks very old and half-digested. This is what you manage to decipher:\n\"ENTRY 25\nI\'ve had such a wonderful idea.\nIn one arena night I earned more kamas than in a week of...\""};
descriptions["20429"]={cn:"这页看起来像某本日志的序。半消化的它看起来非常破旧。尝试找到可以告诉你更多关于它事情的人。\n以下是你看的懂的部分：\n\"第一项\n我：「我想这艘船的主人 - 尼罗。我, 宝石...\"",en:"This page looks like the first entry of a logbook. It looks very old and half-digested. Try and find someone who can tell you more about it. \nThis is what you manage to decipher:\n\"ENTRY 1\nMy word! I seem to be the owner of a boat - the Nyl. Me, Gem...\""};
descriptions["20430"]={cn:"这页看起来像某本日志的第 187 项。半消化的它看起来非常破旧。\n以下是你看的懂的部分：\n\"第 187 项\n我今天去拜访Jan Honning Speck教授, 他似乎...\"",en:"This page looks like entry 187 of a logbook. It looks very old and half-digested. This is what you manage to decipher:\n\"ENTRY 187\nI had a visit from Professor Jan Honning Speck today. It seems he\'s got some...\""};
descriptions["20431"]={cn:"这页看起来像某本日志的第 195 项。半消化的它看起来非常破旧。\n以下是你看的懂的部分：\n\"第 195 项\n难以置信! 太不可思了!\n野性尼罗鳄! 这...这...\"",en:"This page looks like entry 195 of a logbook. It looks very old and half-digested. This is what you manage to decipher:\n\"ENTRY 195\nIncredible! It\'s all incredible!\nWild Crocodyls! It\'s... It\'s...\""};
descriptions["20433"]={cn:"这页看起来像某本日志的第 196 项。半消化的它看起来非常破旧。\n以下是你看的懂的部分：\n\"第 196 项\n几天下来, 他拒绝告诉我更多有关尼罗鳄从哪的详细信息! 真自私阿! 我需要...\"",en:"This page looks like entry 196 of a logbook. It looks very old and half-digested. This is what you manage to decipher:\n\"ENTRY 196\nFor days he\'s refused to give me more information about where the Crocodyls came from! How selfish! I need...\""};
descriptions["20434"]={cn:"这页看起来像某本日志的第 197 项。半消化的它看起来非常破旧。\n以下是你看的懂的部分：\n\"第 197 项\n所以一切都到位了。在七天后, 陷阱将会合上...\"",en:"This page looks like entry 197 of a logbook. It looks very old and half-digested. This is what you manage to decipher:\n\"ENTRY 197\nSo, everything\'s in place. In seven days, the trap will close...\""};
descriptions["20435"]={cn:"这页看起来像某本日志的第 206 项。半消化的它看起来非常破旧。\n以下是你看的懂的部分：\n\"第 206 项\n我是船上的新手, 杰克．利利．史壮, 我带回来了...\"",en:"This page looks like entry 206 of a logbook. It looks very old and half-digested. This is what you manage to decipher:\n\"ENTRY 206\nI\'m the ship\'s apprentice, Jacky Lilye Tstrong, and I\'m taking back the...\""};
descriptions["20436"]={cn:"这页看起来像某本日志的第 207 项。半消化的它看起来非常破旧。\n以下是你看的懂的部分：\n\"第 207 项\n暴风肆虐, 但今早我的第三次远征让我...\"",en:"This page looks like entry 207 of a logbook. It looks very old and half-digested. This is what you manage to decipher:\n\"ENTRY 207\nThe storm rages, but my third expedition this morning allowed me to...\""};
descriptions["20437"]={cn:"这页看起来像某本日志的第 215 项。半消化的它看起来非常破旧。\n以下是你看的懂的部分：\n\"第 215 项\n我还活着。艾卡利菲保佑!\n真不敢相信。不只我...\"",en:"This page looks like entry 215 of a logbook. It looks very old and half-digested. This is what you manage to decipher:\n\"ENTRY 215\nI\'m alive. By Ecaflip!\nIt\'s almost unbelievable. And not only am I...\""};
descriptions["20438"]={cn:"这页看起来像某本日志的第 226 项。半消化的它看起来非常破旧。\n以下是你看的懂的部分：\n\"第 226 项\n三星期! 我到这个岛已经三星期了! 少数生物...\"",en:"This page looks like entry 226 of a logbook. It looks very old and half-digested. This is what you manage to decipher:\n\"ENTRY 226\nThree weeks! Already three weeks that I\'ve been on this island. The few living things...\""};
descriptions["20439"]={cn:"这页看起来像某本日志的第 255 项。半消化的它看起来非常破旧。\n以下是你看的懂的部分：\n\"第 255 项\n我很伤心。一切都是我的错, 我太有自信, 太鲁莽...\"",en:"This page looks like entry 255 of a logbook. It looks very old and half-digested. This is what you manage to decipher:\n\"ENTRY 255\nI\'m hurt. It\'s my fault, I was too confident, too reckless. On my...\""};
descriptions["20440"]={cn:"根据杰克．利利．史壮所言，只要素材运用得当，就能用这个装订套件将尼罗竞技场号的日志装订起来。另外，他说这个东西是他的高博球Boufson制作的...",en:"According to Jacky Lilye Tstrong, this improvised kit should allow you to put the Nyl Arena\'s logbook back together, if used with the right components. On the other hand, he says that it\'s his gobball ball, Boufson, who made it..."};
descriptions["20441"]={cn:"重新装订后的船志看起来够像本真的日志了。拿给杰克．利利．史壮看是不是他要的东西。",en:"This reassembled journal now looks enough like a real logbook. Take it to Jacky Lilye Tstrong to check that it suits him."};
descriptions["20442"]={cn:"尼罗竞技场号的日志，用食人藤的叶子装订而成。这艘船在数十年前运送野生鳄鱼时于月岛撞毁。\n送给杰克．利利．史壮的。",en:"Logbook of the ship, the Nyl Arena, reassembled using Kannivore leaves. The ship was transporting wild Crocodyls, but was wrecked on Moon Island several decades ago.\nGift for Jacky Lilye Tstrong."};
descriptions["20443"]={cn:"这日志的第一部份看来记述着船启程时的事，当时船是在一位名为库克的船长指挥之下。\n你还需要两个部分来把日志装订起来。",en:"This first piece of logbook seems to talk about the ship\'s beginnings, under the command of a certain Captain Crook.\nYou\'ll need two more to put the logbook back together."};
descriptions["20444"]={cn:"这日志的第二部份看来记述着库克船长的不幸遭遇和某个污点。\n你还需要两个部分来把日志装订起来。",en:"This second piece of logbook seems to talk about Captain Crook\'s misadventures, and a certain Speck.\nYou\'ll need two more to put the logbook back together."};
descriptions["20445"]={cn:"这日志的第三部份看来详细探讨着杰克．利利．史壮的失落。\n你还需要两个部分来把日志装订起来。",en:"This third piece of logbook seems to explore Jacky Lilye Tstrong\'s disappointments in details.\nYou\'ll need two more to put the logbook back together."};
descriptions["20447"]={cn:"此卷轴让你重置一个属性页面。\n打开属性页面列表以使用此卷轴，必须在此帐号内有等级至少 51 的角色才能解锁页面。\n此卷轴与帐号绑定，并会在使用后消耗掉。",en:"Lets you reset a Characteristics page.\nGo to the change interface for a Characteristics page. You must have a character of level 51 or higher on your account to unlock this interface.\nThis scroll is linked to the account and will be consumed upon use."};
descriptions["20448"]={cn:"瓶中信:\n\"我在喱维萨附近的一个岛上\"",en:"Message in the bottle:\n\"I\'m on an island off Bilbiza\""};
descriptions["20449"]={cn:"瓶中信:\n\"我建造了海洋宫殿\"",en:"Message in the bottle:\n\"I built the Märine Pälace\""};
descriptions["20450"]={cn:"瓶中信:\n\"有，有人吗……救救我\"",en:"Message in the bottle:\n\"Helllloooo... help me\""};
descriptions["20451"]={cn:"瓶中信:\n\"我饿了。\"",en:"Message in the bottle:\n\"I\'m hungry\""};
descriptions["20452"]={cn:"可以请你跳支舞吗？来吧！\n教会你“B-Box B”表情。",en:"Well, what are you waiting for? Dance!\nThis scroll will teach you the \"Beatbox B\" emote."};
descriptions["20453"]={cn:"可以请你跳支舞吗？来吧！\n教会你“B-Box C”表情。",en:"Well, what are you waiting for? Dance!\nThis scroll will teach you the \"Beatbox C\" emote."};
descriptions["20454"]={cn:"可以请你跳支舞吗？来吧！\n教会你“B-Box D”表情。",en:"Well, what are you waiting for? Dance!\nThis scroll will teach you the \"Beatbox D\" emote."};
descriptions["20455"]={cn:"我抬起我的手臂，*喀啦*！ 我弯曲我的膝盖，然后*喀啦*！ 我扭曲我的脖子，*喀啦*！ 所以，我得出以下结论：你年龄越大，你变得越脆！",en:"I lifted my arms, and *crack*! I bent my knees, and *crack*! I twisted my neck, and *crack*! So, I came to the following conclusion: the older you get, the more cracking you become!"};
descriptions["20456"]={cn:"你周围的水看起来太像女弓箭手了。当你了解了他们的风风雨雨和平稳年代，他们的奇思妙想，以及他们的眼睛反射落日余晖时的美丽时，你就会明白这一点。",en:"The water surrounding you looks too much like a female Cra. It\'s obvious when you know their stormy and calm periods, their whims, and the beauty of their eyes as they reflect the light of the setting sun."};
descriptions["20457"]={cn:"在狼的家里，绵球都知道如何游泳。",en:"In the Boowolf\'s house, Gobballs all know how to swim."};
descriptions["20458"]={cn:"尽你所能地埋葬对手...哦，你做得很好！继续保持！",en:"Burying your rivals as you should... Oh, you do have a nice job! May it last!"};
descriptions["20459"]={cn:"这难道不让人忆起童年吗？",en:"Doesn\'t this bring back childhood memories?"};
descriptions["20460"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["20461"]={cn:"你真的很有天赋：你所要做的就是让他们相信他们成功了，而他们完全靠自己做到了。",en:"You\'ve got real talent: all you had to do was convince them they\'d succeed, and they did so all on their own."};
descriptions["20462"]={cn:"现在，当你在河流下两万里的时候，你就不用为浮上来呼吸空气发愁了。",en:"Now you won\'t have to worry about coming up for air when you\'re 20,000 leagues under the rivers."};
descriptions["20463"]={cn:"全天保持水分！应对海面变化！",en:"Stay hydrated throughout the day! Guaranteed sea mutation!"};
descriptions["20465"]={cn:"这件服装洋溢着善意。",en:"An evolution of your first outfit as a young Incarnate!"};
descriptions["20471"]={cn:"一发提神绷带让你解除疲劳以及所有跟死亡相关的恶心状态！",en:"A Darm Bandage lets you dispel De Darm and all those nasty effects associated with death!"};
descriptions["20472"]={cn:"这件雕像上雕刻的是世界上最伟大的导师之一。",en:"This statuette is on of the greatest mentors the world has ever known."};
descriptions["20473"]={cn:"要是担心出门时忘了戴帽子，那就快来看看这个实用的帽架吧！诶...现在还流行戴帽子么？",en:"So you won\'t forget your hat when you go out, here\'s a convenient Hat Stand. Wait... people still wear hats?"};
descriptions["20474"]={cn:"我的天啊！那是船长的烟斗！...我以为自己无法再听得这么清楚了...",en:"Goodness me! That\'s the captain\'s pipe!... I thought I couldn\'t hear so well any more..."};
descriptions["20475"]={cn:"华生，电话一直在响，怎么没人去接！",en:"Watson, the phone\'s ringin\' but no one ever answers it!"};
descriptions["20476"]={cn:"无论你是导师还是抖S，你都应该配上这套装束。",en:"Whether you\'re a mentor or a torment, you\'ve really deserved this costume."};
descriptions["20477"]={cn:"把这个装饰装备到龙鸟或军鸟身上，毫无疑问：你是一名当之无愧的导师。",en:"By equipping this harness for Dragoturkeys or Dragosteeds, you\'ll leave no doubt: you\'re a qualified Mentor."};
descriptions["20478"]={cn:"你可以使用这个奖章在阿斯图布酒馆内的导师兑奖机兑换奖励。",en:"This token will enable you to obtain Mentorship prizes from the Machine inside Astrub Inn."};
descriptions["20479"]={cn:"你做的不赖！继续保持。",en:"You\'re not doing so bad! Keep it up."};
descriptions["20480"]={cn:"在海洋中浸泡了太长时间后，你的坐骑开始看起来像是小美人鱼。",en:"After soaking in the ocean for too long, your mount is starting to look like the little furmaid."};
descriptions["20481"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with the mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["20482"]={cn:"这种药水提高你所有专业的制作速度50％一个小时。",en:"This potion increases the speed of crafting in all your professions by 50% for one hour."};
descriptions["20483"]={cn:"这种药水提高你所有专业的种植和收获的速度50％一个小时。",en:"This potion increases the speed of planting and harvesting in all your professions by 50% for one hour."};
descriptions["20484"]={cn:"这药水会把你变成一座雄伟的沙雕城堡。不过要注意，你不能动了！",en:"This potion will turn you into a majestic Sänd Cästle. Be warned, though: you won\'t be able to move!"};
descriptions["20485"]={cn:"一种能让你在海洋宫殿里挖掘宝藏的铲子。",en:"A shovel which lets you find treasure by digging in the Märine Pälace."};
descriptions["20486"]={cn:"这份潦草的手稿试图说明前往黑色史盖特处所需要踩的地砖顺序。",en:"These scribbles are trying to explain the order in which you\'ll need to step on the tiles to reach the Bläckskate."};
descriptions["20488"]={cn:"420 卡玛，因爱铸就。",en:"420 little Kamas, minted with love."};
descriptions["20489"]={cn:"510 卡玛，因爱铸就。",en:"510 little Kamas, minted with love."};
descriptions["20490"]={cn:"600 卡玛，因爱铸就。",en:"600 little Kamas, minted with love."};
descriptions["20491"]={cn:"10,600 卡玛，因爱铸就。",en:"10,600 little Kamas, minted with love."};
descriptions["20492"]={cn:"11,400 卡玛，因爱铸就。",en:"11,400 little Kamas, minted with love."};
descriptions["20493"]={cn:"你想卷入新的浪潮吗？这个卷轴会让你的梦想成真！",en:"Do you want to get caught up in a new wave movement? This scroll will make your dreams come true!"};
descriptions["20494"]={cn:"没必要在酷暑中建造你的沙雕城堡。只要把你自己变成这样，就会更快更容易！",en:"No need to build your Sänd Cästle in the scorching heat. Just turn yourself into one, it\'s much faster and easier!"};
descriptions["20495"]={cn:"无论何时何地，只要你愿意，都可以插上你的国旗！",en:"Plant your nation\'s flag wherever and whenever you like!"};
descriptions["20496"]={cn:"现在你可以在充满凉风和海鲜的庇护袋里放松一下了。",en:"Now you can chill out in your Haven Bag full of cool air and seafood."};
descriptions["20497"]={cn:"A trophy representing 查尔斯·亨利·维勒登mechanically improved variant of Tutaur\'Kama the Mechamummy, whom you defeated.",en:"A trophy representing Charles-Henri of Vileardent\'s mechanically improved variant of Tutaur\'Kama the Mechamummy, whom you defeated."};
descriptions["20498"]={cn:"喵喵曾被认为是能护佑人们的神圣动物，非常受人崇敬，并且有很多雕像。",en:"Bow Meows were once considered to be sacred, protective animals. They were highly venerated, and many effigies of them existed."};
descriptions["20499"]={cn:"这块石碑是是对于土元素的精准复刻，曾被用于查尔斯·亨利·德·维勒登最爱看的悲喜剧中。",en:"This stele is a very faithful reproduction of the element earth, used in a tragi-comedy much enjoyed by Charles-Henri of Vileardent."};
descriptions["20500"]={cn:"这块石碑是是对于火元素的精准复刻，曾被用于查尔斯·亨利·德·维勒登最爱看的悲喜剧中。",en:"This stele is a very faithful reproduction of the element fire, used in a tragi-comedy much enjoyed by Charles-Henri of Vileardent."};
descriptions["20501"]={cn:"这块石碑是是对于水元素的精准复刻，曾被用于查尔斯·亨利·德·维勒登最爱看的悲喜剧中。",en:"This stele is a very faithful reproduction of the element water, used in a tragi-comedy much enjoyed by Charles-Henri of Vileardent."};
descriptions["20502"]={cn:"一个小小的金罐子，能够陶冶你的情操。",en:"A small, Golden Jar to discreetly refine your insides."};
descriptions["20503"]={cn:"西迪莫特公司械肯-0 的广告海报的第 1 部分。",en:"The first part of the advertising poster for the manufacturing of Sidimotes & Co.\'s Mechan-0s."};
descriptions["20504"]={cn:"这块静止不动的表通过指针在太阳下的影子来显示时间。",en:"This silent, stationary clock shows the solar time using the movement of the hand\'s shadow."};
descriptions["20505"]={cn:"查尔斯·亨利·维勒登的展示柜之一。",en:"One of Charles-Henri of Vileardent\'s display cabinets."};
descriptions["20506"]={cn:"这显然是一个豆芙的的金底座复刻品，出自一个只有查尔斯·亨利才能找到的珠宝匠之手。",en:"This is obviously a gold-plated replica of a Dofus, made by a jeweler whose location only Charles-Henri knows."};
descriptions["20507"]={cn:"这个工人套装是查尔斯·亨利·维勒登的工厂的官方工作服。",en:"This Worker Costume is the official work costume of Charles-Henri of Vileardent\'s Factory: Sidimotes & Co."};
descriptions["20509"]={cn:"完成国家任务第四章“不可触及”后获得的奖励。",en:"Title awarded after having completed \"The Untouchables\" in chapter 4 of the Nations Quest."};
descriptions["20510"]={cn:"完成国家任务第四章“Con a la carte”后获得的奖励。",en:"Title awarded after having completed \"Con à la carte\" in chapter 4 of the Nations Quest."};
descriptions["20511"]={cn:"完成国家任务第四章“致命引力”后获得的奖励。",en:"Title awarded after having completed \"Dangerous Seduction\" in chapter 4 of the Nations Quest."};
descriptions["20513"]={cn:"完成国家任务第四章“最终威胁”后获得的奖励。",en:"Title awarded after having completed \"Final Threat\" in chapter 4 of the Nations Quest."};
descriptions["20514"]={cn:"完成国家任务第四章“十面埋伏”后获得的奖励。",en:"Title awarded after having completed \"House of Flying Daggers\" in chapter 4 of the Nations Quest."};
descriptions["20515"]={cn:"完成国家任务第四章“触碰逆鳞”后获得的奖励。",en:"Title awarded after having completed \"Hit a Nerve\" in chapter 4 of the Nations Quest."};
descriptions["20516"]={cn:"完成国家任务第四章“愤怒的守卫们”后获得的奖励。",en:"Title awarded after having completed \"Ruffled Guardians\" in chapter 4 of the Nations Quest."};
descriptions["20517"]={cn:"当进行人工作业时，佩戴适当的护眼道具是必须的，哪怕你只是把镜片卡在头顶上。",en:"When doing manual work, wearing appropriate eye protection is obligatory. Even if it\'s classier perched on your head than in front of your eyes."};
descriptions["20525"]={cn:"西迪莫特公司械肯-0的广告海报的第2部分。",en:"The second part of the advertising poster for the manufacturing of Sidimotes & Co.\'s Mechan-0s."};
descriptions["20527"]={cn:"这火焰能重燃你即将熄灭的热情，照亮你的黑暗。",en:"This fire will rekindle your half-extinguished flame and illuminate your dark days."};
descriptions["20528"]={cn:"查尔斯·亨利维勒登的\"Sidimotes & Co.\"工厂旗子。",en:"A Flag in the colors of Charles-Henri of Vileardent\'s \"Sidimotes & Co.\" Factory."};
descriptions["20529"]={cn:"你是个自豪的爱国者吗，那么就一直穿着这件时装吧！",en:"Are you a proudly patriotic? Then wear this costume all the time!"};
descriptions["20530"]={cn:"别再试了，你只会卡在烟囱里。",en:"No, don\'t bother trying; you\'ll only get stuck in the chimney."};
descriptions["20531"]={cn:"一件用于赞美死者的节日时装。",en:"A festive costume to glorify the dead of our world."};
descriptions["20532"]={cn:"使用它能为一个路人进行急救。",en:"This emote lets you give first aid to the first passer-by."};
descriptions["20533"]={cn:"这是一个暖心的礼物。",en:"A heartwarming gift."};
descriptions["20534"]={cn:"这个药水能让你变成一块美味的圣诞饼干。",en:"This potion will transform you into a scrumptious Kwismas biscuit."};
descriptions["20535"]={cn:"一张用来为死者拜访面包和各种祭品的桌子。",en:"A table on which bread is shared and various offerings to the dead are prepared."};
descriptions["20536"]={cn:"你将会灵魂出窍，睡得跟个死人一样。",en:"You\'ll leave your body and sleep like the dead."};
descriptions["20537"]={cn:"由亡灵脂完美制成的一盏永不熄灭的蜡烛。",en:"An eternal candle, perfectly encrusted in copal resin."};
descriptions["20538"]={cn:"一种失传了的游戏，在死者之日被拿了出来。",en:"A game lost to the annals, taken out and placed on the table on days of the dead."};
descriptions["20539"]={cn:"这个碗柜里装满了丧命者装备和新鲜的尸体。",en:"This cupboard may contain an arsenal of bereavement outfits, close-range weapons, or freshly-gathered corpses."};
descriptions["20540"]={cn:"这个屏风用木头和一些剪成各种图案的彩纸做成。",en:"This display is made of wood and little bits of colored paper cut into various patterned shapes."};
descriptions["20541"]={cn:"这些花一般都用于亡灵节时摆放在坟墓前。",en:"These flowers are often placed on tombs during the Día de los Muertos festival."};
descriptions["20542"]={cn:"在死者的节日里十分常见的娃娃。",en:"A doll familiar to the festival of the dead."};
descriptions["20543"]={cn:"不要忘了和他们度过的那些时光。",en:"So as not to forget important and unimportant moments spent at their side."};
descriptions["20544"]={cn:"一个方便你穿戴寿衣的地方。",en:"A place to put away your bedding and shrouds."};
descriptions["20545"]={cn:"带有亡灵节的标志色，可以装备于战斗坐骑。",en:"A Dragosteed skin in the colors of the day of the dead."};
descriptions["20546"]={cn:"这套神秘配色版坐骑装饰会让你想边唱边飞向星空。它或许适合用来装扮一只龙鸟。",en:"This Dragosteed skin in mystical colors makes you want to fly among the stars singing."};
descriptions["20547"]={cn:"宠物染料可以于宠物设定介面中更改。此物品已无用处，可以将其分解掉。",en:"Pet colorings can be changed in the pet settings interface. This item is obsolete; you can recycle it."};
descriptions["20548"]={cn:"这到底是颗糖果还是个南瓜头！？",en:"Is this a candy or a pumpkinned face?!"};
descriptions["20549"]={cn:"这里好冷啊，你不觉得么0.0？！",en:"This scroll will teach you the \"Blizzard Aura\" emote."};
descriptions["20550"]={cn:"原来这就是斯冬妮娅大裙子下面藏着的东西么！运气好的话，这个鞋号正合你的脚。",en:"So that\'s what Sydonia was hiding under her big dress! With a bit of luck, you\'ll take the same shoe size."};
descriptions["20551"]={cn:"穿了这双靴子，你才真算得上是扎根于沃土。",en:"Wearing such boots, you\'ll truly be at one with the ground."};
descriptions["20552"]={cn:"虽然看起来不怎么漂亮，但这顶葡萄藤之冠可是强大力量的象征。",en:"It may not look very impressive, but this crown of vines is a symbol of great power."};
descriptions["20553"]={cn:"你把这玩意儿戴头上的唯一理由就是以丑遮丑。",en:"The only reason you wore this on your head was to hide your ugliness with an even uglier face."};
descriptions["20554"]={cn:"斯冬妮娅就是从这件珠宝中得到力量的么？不管怎样，它散发出许多热量。",en:"Is this jewel where Sydonia got her power? In any case, it gives off a lot of heat."};
descriptions["20555"]={cn:"别吃这个护符！上面的葡萄粒是假的！",en:"Don\'t eat this amulet! Its grape seeds are fake!"};
descriptions["20556"]={cn:"这个腰带通过把刺扎进皮肤里来起到塑形健美的作用，痛并快乐着。",en:"This belt keeps you in shape by sticking loads of little spikes into your skin. Painful, but effective."};
descriptions["20557"]={cn:"摸了摸裤裆，然后把什么放到了嘴里。",en:"It\'s tempting to pick this stem hanging between your legs."};
descriptions["20558"]={cn:"这个缠腰有一股弄弄的乡村气息，你是有多久没洗过了？",en:"This loincloth has a strong countryside smell. When was the last time you washed it?"};
descriptions["20559"]={cn:"这件看似简朴的护肩实际上边缘非常锋利。",en:"These simple-looking epaulettes are actually very sharp around the edges."};
descriptions["20560"]={cn:"这件植物护肩非常实用，不过别忘了三天一浇水，还有多进行光合作用。",en:"These vegetal epaulettes are effective, but don\'t forget to water them every three days and to give them plenty of sunshine."};
descriptions["20561"]={cn:"有点硌得慌，穿着它脖子别乱动。",en:"Slightly rigid, this armor shows everyone which neck of the woods you come from!"};
descriptions["20562"]={cn:"多练几回，这戒指比瓶起子好使多了。",en:"With enough practice, this ring can take out corks just as easily as Chafer Teeth."};
descriptions["20563"]={cn:"这枚戒指携带着Viticultists的气息，证明着你战胜了他。",en:"This ring carries the sign of the Viticultists. It proves you beat them."};
descriptions["20564"]={cn:"这翅膀没法让你上天，但是他能表明你不惧怕魔族。",en:"This wing won\'t make you fly, but it\'ll show everyone you\'re not afraid of Shushus."};
descriptions["20565"]={cn:"一个魔族皮制成的包，这可是能拿来向其他探险家显摆的玩意儿。",en:"A Shushu-skin bag, now that\'s something that\'ll impress other adventurers!"};
descriptions["20566"]={cn:"用魔界之火打造，这把剑会灼烧你的双手，但这是值得的。",en:"Forged in the fires of the Shustuft Crust, this blade will burn your hands, but it\'s worth it."};
descriptions["20567"]={cn:"这武器强大到让你十分满意，但是你老是忍不住想：这TM是谁的头骨啊？",en:"This ring is satisfyingly powerful, but one question haunts you: who does this skull belong to?"};
descriptions["20568"]={cn:"这锤子里装满了红酒，一锤子把对手砸醉。",en:"This hammer is filled with wine, to give your opponents a nice hangover."};
descriptions["20569"]={cn:"这把剑的剑柄由藤木做成，不过剑刃可不是！",en:"This sword\'s pommel is made of wood, but its blade isn\'t!"};
descriptions["20570"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with the mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["20571"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with the mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["20573"]={cn:"使用地下城的兑奖机器用硬币换取流弊的装备。",en:"Use the machine across from the dungeon to exchange your tokens for fantastic rewards."};
descriptions["20574"]={cn:"能给你的发明加上点装饰性。",en:"Something to bring a decorative touch to your creations."};
descriptions["20575"]={cn:"别和白色织布一块儿洗。",en:"Do not wash with White Fabric."};
descriptions["20576"]={cn:"点击两下来把整组古代资源转换成新的资源。古代资源需尽快使用，它们在未来的更新里会被移除。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["20577"]={cn:"你可以根据魔族尾巴的尺寸来估测出它们的力量，起码它们想让你这么认为。",en:"A Shushu\'s power can be measured by the size of its tail. At least, that\'s what they\'d have you believe."};
descriptions["20578"]={cn:"这座雕塑可不会给你家的客人什么好脸色看。",en:"This statue may not give the warmest welcome when you\'ve got guests."};
descriptions["20579"]={cn:"爬满了伯爵的坟墓~",en:"This unique vegetal touch will make your garden look great, but also fruitless."};
descriptions["20580"]={cn:"一个用来和朋友共度良宵的完美器材。",en:"A perfect device for your little evenings with your friends."};
descriptions["20581"]={cn:"这盏灯营造出一种令人不安的氛围，可你要是把它关了，你就得置身于恐怖的黑暗。",en:"This lamp gives off a worrying ambiance, but if you turn it off, you\'ll be left in the dark."};
descriptions["20582"]={cn:"把你的对手变成南瓜，估计不行...",en:"Transform your adversaries into a Pumpkwin, or not."};
descriptions["20583"]={cn:"拥抱喵鱼是一种喜欢抱抱的喵鱼，鱼如其名。",en:"The Cuddly Bow Meow Fish is a variety of Bow Meow Fish that loves a good cuddle, hence its name."};
descriptions["20584"]={cn:"在食物里多放点，齁死你讨厌的那些客人们。",en:"Put enough of this in your food and your guests will be too busy trying not to throw up to hear the snide comments you keep making about them."};
descriptions["20585"]={cn:"我要达到火焰都无法达到的温度，我要烧焦着悲惨的世界，我才是燃烧的大师！",en:"I\'ll succeed where Iron didn\'t. I\'m going to bleed this miserable world dry, and ensure my place as true master of the Burning Mine!"};
descriptions["20587"]={cn:"有一个童话故事讲，吉瓦把这朵花送给一个婴儿，让他不要哭。从那时起，在新生儿的婴儿床上放一个这个就成了传统。",en:"There\'s a children\'s story that says that Jiva offered this flower to a baby to stop it from crying. Ever since, it\'s been traditional to pop one into newborns\' cribs."};
descriptions["20588"]={cn:"弹完钢琴的吉伯特·栗木站了起来。这句话看似平常，但对我来说意义重大，因为这老瞎子连琴键都看不见，弹得别提多烂了。",en:"Gilbert Chestnut played the piano standing up; while this is just a minor detail to you, it has great meaning to me. What\'s more, he played it really badly because he couldn\'t see the keys."};
descriptions["20589"]={cn:"这种木头是中空的，你可以冬天套在身上来保暖。然而跟宝宝榛木这个名字有什么关系呢。",en:"This wood is so hollow you could put it on to keep warm on those cold, winter nights. However, that\'s nowhere near as cute as a real babez."};
descriptions["20590"]={cn:"曾经，菊芋根因为原产地而被人们叫做“阿玛克纳松露”，现在，只有其中的精品才能这么叫。",en:"Once, Artichoke Roots were called \"Amakna Truffles\", due to where they come from. Now, only the prettiest examples bear this name."};
descriptions["20591"]={cn:"将你的装备（武器除外）能力值套用为此等级区间内装备的平均值，你必须分配技能点数及装备武器。",en:"Replaces the stats you have from equipment (excluding weapons) with AVERAGE stats at this level. You must distribute your skills and equip a weapon."};
descriptions["20592"]={cn:"将你的装备（武器除外）能力值套用为此等级区间内装备的最高值，你必须分配技能点数及装备武器。",en:"Replaces the stats you have from equipment (excluding weapons) with MAX stats at this level. You must distribute your skills and equip a weapon."};
descriptions["20593"]={cn:"将你的装备（武器除外）能力值套用为此等级区间内装备的平均值，你必须分配技能点数及装备武器。",en:"Replaces the stats you have from equipment (excluding weapons) with AVERAGE stats at this level. You must distribute your skills and equip a weapon."};
descriptions["20594"]={cn:"将你的装备（武器除外）能力值套用为此等级区间内装备的最高值，你必须分配技能点数及装备武器。",en:"Replaces the stats you have from equipment (excluding weapons) with MAX stats at this level. You must distribute your skills and equip a weapon."};
descriptions["20595"]={cn:"巫师出售这些犄角的粉末给游客，宣称可以为他们带来好运。问题是，它会引发绵球发情...",en:"Sorcerers sell tourists these horns in powdered form to bring them luck. The problem is, it also attracts Gobblettes in heat..."};
descriptions["20596"]={cn:"这个称号奖励给那些在第二次混沌中活下来的勇敢冒险者们，只有真正的英雄才能从这场大战中挺过来。",en:"This title is awarded to the brave adventurers who survived the second chaos. Only true heroes still stand after this great battle."};
descriptions["20597"]={cn:"你拍死了差不多100只吃饱了的滋滋才收集到的这个量！",en:"About a hundred Moskitos were crushed to collect this blood!"};
descriptions["20598"]={cn:"一首哲学诗讲述了如何处理栗树上的栗子，亦或是一些超现实的想象，没人真的知道。",en:"A philosophical poem about what to do with the fruit of the chestnut tree, or about Oneself and the image that Others have of use; no one really knows."};
descriptions["20599"]={cn:"丝滑柔软的毛皮...长满了虱子。",en:"It\'s still got silky, soft fur... full of lice."};
descriptions["20600"]={cn:"算你走运！起码你不用去扯开它的爪子！",en:"You should be happy! You didn\'t have to deal with its claws!"};
descriptions["20601"]={cn:"充满了粘胶，你很难找到放在包里的东西。完全不用担心东西被偷。",en:"All the mucus sloshing around inside this pouch will make finding your stuff pretty difficult. But it\'ll also deter any potential thieves from taking it!"};
descriptions["20603"]={cn:"篮子里有些什么？起司！",en:"What have you got in this basket, then? Cheese, cheese-uh-huh!"};
descriptions["20604"]={cn:"你什么时候开始穿奶奶的旧衣服了？",en:"When did you start dressing in your grandmother\'s clothes?"};
descriptions["20605"]={cn:"胶水是物品制作中的理想原料。可以通过完成6-20级的地图限时任务获得。",en:"Souper-Glou is the ideal ingredient to assemble your items. You can get it as a reward for the level 6 to 20 Environmental Quests."};
descriptions["20606"]={cn:"胶水是物品制作中的理想原料。 可以通过完成21-35级的地图限时任务获得。",en:"Souper-Glou is the ideal ingredient to assemble your items. You can get it as a reward for the level 21 to 35 Environmental Quests."};
descriptions["20651"]={cn:"这些腿还在跟着音乐的节奏抖动着，像被麦卡尔杰克逊附体一样。",en:"These legs still move to certain musical sounds. Put simply, you might get a surprise if you think you\'re Mika El Jacq-Son!"};
descriptions["20652"]={cn:"锭是物品制作中的理想原料。通过0级挖矿制作，可用于0-20级装备等用品制作。",en:"A solid structure for your products; however, you shouldn\'t expect any more from this steel."};
descriptions["20653"]={cn:"锭是物品制作中的理想原料。通过10级挖矿制作，可用于21-35级装备等用品制作。",en:"This steel is the most flexible of types of steel; in other words, not very flexible."};
descriptions["20654"]={cn:"精华是物品制作中的理想原料。通过0级畜牧制作，可用于0-20级装备等用品制作。",en:"A vial with a mystic look, but which contains nothing but the essence of the most primitive of monsters."};
descriptions["20655"]={cn:"这份精华包含了怪物的灵魂，能把力量注入几乎所有类型的物品。",en:"This essence contains monsters\' souls, and can instill their power into almost all types of items."};
descriptions["20656"]={cn:"树蜘蛛皮的外层被木头加固过。",en:"This is a type of skin, reinforced with wood, which covers Treechnees\' bodies."};
descriptions["20657"]={cn:"让你所有的家具结实稳固。",en:"This bracket will help all your furniture hold on tight."};
descriptions["20659"]={cn:"纤维是物品制作中的理想原料。通过0级裁缝制作，可用于0-20级装备等用品制作。",en:"Some people are made of a maternal fiber, and other people have this fiber."};
descriptions["20660"]={cn:"纤维是物品制作中的理想原料。通过10级裁缝制作，可用于21-35级装备等用品制作。",en:"This enriched fiber possesses great culture, seeing that\'s what it\'s made from."};
descriptions["20661"]={cn:"宝石是物品制作中的理想原料。通过10级珠宝制作，可用于21-35级装备等用品制作。",en:"It still isn\'t the most precious gem ever, but it is pretty."};
descriptions["20662"]={cn:"护板是物品制作中的理想原料。通过10级制甲制作，可用于21-35级装备等用品制作。",en:"Drop everything to leave and not come back."};
descriptions["20663"]={cn:"香料是物品制作中的理想原料。通过10级厨师制作，可用于21-35级装备等用品制作。",en:"With this, your dishes could raise the dead in Astrub Cemetery, or your fallen teammates."};
descriptions["20664"]={cn:"香油是物品制作中的理想原料。通过10级面包制作，可用于21-35级装备等用品制作。",en:"On oil of the most rudimentary kind, as its name suggests. Did you really need to read this to be convinced of it?"};
descriptions["20665"]={cn:"手柄是物品制作中的理想原料。通过10级武器制作，可用于21-35级装备等用品制作。",en:"If you stack them properly, it seems it\'s possible to make a pile of wood out of them."};
descriptions["20666"]={cn:"有了这个强大的戒指就知足吧！一点一滴才是真。",en:"With this great ring, you\'ll be happy being happy! It\'s the little things that count."};
descriptions["20667"]={cn:"这双靴子穿起来太舒服了，你觉得非常的满足，然而你的敌人好像不是很稀罕这个。",en:"These shoes are so comfortable, you can\'t help but be satisfied with them. Your enemies might not be quite so content if you decide to give them the boot, though."};
descriptions["20668"]={cn:"你可以说你需要布鲁塔的力量，所以需要这个犄角！",en:"You could say that you needed the strength of Brutas to get this horn!"};
descriptions["20669"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few drops should suffice."};
descriptions["20670"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few drops should suffice."};
descriptions["20671"]={cn:"与血压不同，树人生气时不会使树液上升。",en:"Rising sap doesn\'t make Treechnees mad, unlike Twelvians."};
descriptions["20672"]={cn:"使用地下城门口的兑奖机兑换流弊的装备，基础硬币适用于：啾啾兑奖机、树人兑奖机、骷髅兑奖机。",en:"Use the following machines to exchange your tokens for fantastic rewards: Piwi, Treechnee, Raised Skeletons."};
descriptions["20675"]={cn:"一条细而多毛的腿。碰它一下的话，它还会动来动去的，有点瘆得慌。",en:"A very hairy but thin leg. When stroked, it keeps moving and seems to be full of life, which is a little disconcerting."};
descriptions["20676"]={cn:"咕咕羽毛几乎和皇家啾啾羽毛一样，是几乎。",en:"Googoo Feathers are almost as magic as those from the Royal Piwi. Almost."};
descriptions["20677"]={cn:"这是树干么？还是条腿？木有人知道。",en:"Is it a branch? Is it a leg? No one really knows."};
descriptions["20678"]={cn:"把骨头磨碎成粉；现在这已经是一个老奶奶常用的食谱了。",en:"Making powder by grinding bones; now that\'s a good old grandmother\'s recipe!"};
descriptions["20679"]={cn:"这皮的主人不喝酒，不抽烟，而且还有练气功。",en:"After preparing this great Tofire Skin, you\'ll be nothing but skin and bone!"};
descriptions["20681"]={cn:"为帮助引导后一代人的冒险家授予的称号。",en:"Title awarded to adventurers that have helped guide the future generations."};
descriptions["20682"]={cn:"你现在可以一边钓凤尾鱼一边自问自答各种困难的问题了，看起来你也别无选择。",en:"You\'ll have all the time to ask yourself difficult questions while fishing for Anchovies. It\'s not like you have the choice, either."};
descriptions["20683"]={cn:"嚼这个能清新口气，交个PY吧~",en:"Chew this for extra-fresh breath."};
descriptions["20684"]={cn:"作为Belle Epoque州的粥长，弗朗西斯死于吃水果时搞混了苹朵木跟苹朵。仔细观察的话，你就能发现这块木头上的牙印。",en:"Great Governor of the Belle Epoque, Francis died from mixing up Apis and Apiwood while tasting them. If you look closely, you should be able to see a few teethmarks."};
descriptions["20685"]={cn:"这种麦秸是专门用来做成流奶和萝卜叽饮料的吸管的。This straw is used to make tubes to siphon Mimilk- and Cawwot-based drinks.",en:"This straw is used to make tubes to siphon Mimilk- and Cawwot-based drinks."};
descriptions["20686"]={cn:"这块悲惨的矿石在淬炼时发出的惨叫声让你过耳不忘...“雅蠛蝶eeeeeeeeeee!”",en:"You can still here the dreadful screams of this poor ore while hitting it to extract it... \"TOOOOOT! TOOOOOOOT!\""};
descriptions["20687"]={cn:"为完成 2016 年 10 月 Boss 大挑战的冒险者颁发的称号。",en:"Title awarded to adventurers that have completed the Boss Smasher Event, October 2016."};
descriptions["20688"]={cn:"为完成 2016 年 11 月 Boss 大挑战的冒险者颁发的称号。",en:"Title awarded to adventurers that have completed the Boss Smasher Event, November 2016."};
descriptions["20689"]={cn:"为完成 2016 年 12 月 Boss 大挑战的冒险者颁发的称号。",en:"Title awarded to adventurers that have completed the Boss Smasher Event, December 2016."};
descriptions["20690"]={cn:"这个称号是给赢得了Efrim伺服器上夏季联赛的玩家。",en:"This title is given to players who won the Summer Tournament on the Efrim server."};
descriptions["20691"]={cn:"重置所有的属性页面。",en:"Lets you reset all your Characteristics pages."};
descriptions["20692"]={cn:"你已经在竞技场中证明了自己的强大实力，现在你可以昂首阔步的迈向十二世界了！",en:"You proved yourself to be stronger than the others in the Back to Arena tournament. Now you can strut around in the World of Twelve!"};
descriptions["20693"]={cn:"能力越大，责任越大。",en:"With great power comes great responsibility."};
descriptions["20709"]={cn:"泡泡，泡泡，弹弹，跳跳...",en:"Bubble, bubble, recoil and stumble..."};
descriptions["20710"]={cn:"无时无刻不在折磨你的耳膜。",en:"It\'ll never stop breaking your eardrums."};
descriptions["20711"]={cn:"这个碗柜里珍藏着最美味的鸡尾酒，绝对能让你度过一个美妙的万圣节，别贪杯哦~",en:"This cupboard contains only the best cocktails to liven up your Al Howin festivities! Consume in moderation."};
descriptions["20712"]={cn:"如果你想假装成为一个巫师，你肯定需要一个桌子，可以处理各种危险液体的泄漏，不然你几乎每天必须换一个新的桌子！",en:"If you want to have a go at pretending to be a Sorcerer, you definitely need a table that can handle all sorts of dangerous liquid spills, otherwise you\'ll have to get a new one practically every day!"};
descriptions["20713"]={cn:"这个卷轴让你学会表情“神秘卡牌”",en:"This scroll will teach you the \"Mystery Card\" emote."};
descriptions["20715"]={cn:"一旦你把这些小精灵释放出来后，它们就会依附到最近的人活着物体上直到消失。",en:"Once these little fairies have been released, there\'s only one thing they want to do: cling on to the nearest person or item until they fade away."};
descriptions["20717"]={cn:"你可以拿辛苦赢来的奖章换取装备。",en:"You can trade in this hard-won token for pieces of equipment."};
descriptions["20718"]={cn:"从诺戈背上掉落的一片龙鳞。",en:"A scale fallen from Nogord\'s back."};
descriptions["20719"]={cn:"龙鳞绣腰襦，葳蕤自生光。",en:"A belt made of solid dragon scales, shimmering with an iridescent sheen."};
descriptions["20720"]={cn:"这枚宝贵的棱晶龙蛋来自诺戈翼龙，一条过去的幼龙。",en:"The precious Prismatic Dofus of Nogord Wungleezared, a minor dragon from the past."};
descriptions["20721"]={cn:"轻便易携，在外冒险或同岳母大人野餐之必备佳品。\n展开仅需2秒！",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with the mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["20722"]={cn:"这对肩甲布满尖刺，很上档次又能威吓敌人。",en:"Bristling with sharp spikes, these epaulettes give both classy and formidable style."};
descriptions["20723"]={cn:"一件沉重的胸甲，意在模仿棱晶龙强壮的身躯。穿上效果一定惊人。",en:"A heavy breastplate imitating the muscular torso of a Prismatic Dragon. A surprising effect is guaranteed."};
descriptions["20724"]={cn:"这件外套用龙鳞经特殊手法交错编织而成，可谓巧夺天工。",en:"A coat of amazing finesse, with a very special intertwining of Dragon scales."};
descriptions["20725"]={cn:"由一位神秘铁匠用龙鳞铸成，此头盔令敌人闻风丧胆。",en:"Forged from dragon scales by a mythical blacksmith, this helm is formidably effective."};
descriptions["20726"]={cn:"高品质护腿，深受弓手们的喜爱。",en:"Shin pads of high quality, highly prized by archers."};
descriptions["20727"]={cn:"一块充满超能量的护符。",en:"An amulet with overpowered powers..."};
descriptions["20728"]={cn:"小小一枚戒指中蕴藏着狂暴兽性之力。",en:"A small ring harboring a violent, beastly power."};
descriptions["20729"]={cn:"这把品质超群的弓的塑造过程不走寻常路。据说它是往昔的龙的魔法创造出来的。",en:"This bow of extraordinary quality has been shaped in a completely unfamiliar way. It\'s said that it was created by the magic of a dragon from the past."};
descriptions["20730"]={cn:"一枚佩戴后拥有惊人抗性的戒指。",en:"A ring which makes its wearer surprisingly resistant."};
descriptions["20731"]={cn:"这条非同小可的皮带是由龙鳞做成的，佩戴者会瞬间拥有令人闻风丧胆的卑鄙技能。",en:"This belt, crafted from dragon scales, will give its bearer formidably sneaky skills."};
descriptions["20732"]={cn:"龙鳞的强化让这件坚固的皮甲变得柔软，而龙鳞间奔流的上古魔力使胸甲的效果更为强大。",en:"A robust leather reinforced with dragon scales, making it supple and strengthening its effects using the ancient magic which traverses the scales."};
descriptions["20733"]={cn:"模仿棱晶龙健硕的翅膀而造的这把锋利的斧子，会成为你血拼沙场的重要战友。",en:"Imitating the wing of a Prismatic Dragon, this particularly sharp axe will be an important ally in wild and epic battles."};
descriptions["20734"]={cn:"这条项链的取材来自于究极强龙的爪子与鳞片，因而它充满了魔力。",en:"This amulet is crafted from the claws and scales of an ultra-powerful dragon, thereby giving undeniable magical properties."};
descriptions["20735"]={cn:"“你为什么治疗的这么熟练啊！你到底给别人治疗了几次？”“我可以告诉你，无可奉告。我身经百战见的多了。”",en:"A great cape, spotted with prismatic reflections which give powerful powers to its wearer."};
descriptions["20736"]={cn:"美丽记忆，永久珍藏。",en:"A nice trophy for your personal collection."};
descriptions["20737"]={cn:"穿上这件时装简直让人羡慕得傻掉。",en:"This costume can stupefy your opponent with admiration."};
descriptions["20738"]={cn:"这件时装你看上去没有头，吓得人见鬼一样撒腿就跑。",en:"This costume will certainly make you lose your head, and others will flee you like the plague."};
descriptions["20739"]={cn:"这件时装将带你到世界的尽头。",en:"This costume will take you to the ends of the World."};
descriptions["20740"]={cn:"这件时装会引出你的黑暗面。",en:"This costume will bring out your dark side."};
descriptions["20741"]={cn:"单体精通地穴兽坐骑",en:"A Drheller trained to fight against a single enemy."};
descriptions["20742"]={cn:"范围精通地穴兽坐骑",en:"A Drheller trained to fight groups of enemies."};
descriptions["20743"]={cn:"近战精通地穴兽坐骑",en:"A drheller specialized in the art of melee fighting."};
descriptions["20744"]={cn:"远程精通地穴兽坐骑",en:"A Drheller trained to fight from a distance."};
descriptions["20745"]={cn:"一个酷洛配色的地穴兽造型。",en:"A Drheller skin in the colors of the Krosmoz."};
descriptions["20746"]={cn:"这个地穴兽的造型浸透了创生力的能量。",en:"This Drheller skin is steeped in Wakfu energy."};
descriptions["20747"]={cn:"这个地穴兽的造型浸透了毁灭的能量。",en:"This Drheller skin is steeped in Stasis energy."};
descriptions["20748"]={cn:"一个黑暗弗拉德配色的地穴兽造型。",en:"A Drheller skin in the colors of Dark Vlad."};
descriptions["20749"]={cn:"普通的地穴兽",en:"A Drheller among so many others!"};
descriptions["20752"]={cn:"这个奖章可以在阿斯图布酒馆的原型兑奖机中，交换相对应等级区间的奖章。",en:"This token can be exchanged for tokens of the same level group in the Modulox Machine inside Astrub Tavern."};
descriptions["20753"]={cn:"使用这个将激活或取消终结者。这不是一件消耗品。它会随机激活一种终结者。",en:"Using this will activate or deactivate the Finisher. The item is not consumed. Random selection among all active Finishers."};
descriptions["20754"]={cn:"使用这个将激活或取消终结者。这不是一件消耗品。它会随机激活一种终结者。",en:"Using this will activate or deactivate the Finisher. The item is not consumed. Random selection among all active Finishers."};
descriptions["20755"]={cn:"使用这个将激活或取消终结者。这不是一件消耗品。它会随机激活一种终结者。",en:"Using this will activate or deactivate the Finisher. The item is not consumed. Random selection among all active Finishers."};
descriptions["20756"]={cn:"使用这个将激活或取消终结者。这不是一件消耗品。它会随机激活一种终结者。",en:"Using this will activate or deactivate the Finisher. The item is not consumed. Random selection among all active Finishers."};
descriptions["20757"]={cn:"它是猴王的一种特殊变种，月神肩甲的效果并没有减少。",en:"A variant of the very specialized version originating from the Monkey King, these Moon Epaulettes are no less effective."};
descriptions["20758"]={cn:"使用地下城对面的机器，用你的奖章交换绝赞奖赏。",en:"Use the machine across from the dungeon to exchange your tokens for fantastic rewards."};
descriptions["20759"]={cn:"这一小块幼龙皮真的很柔软。",en:"This little Wyrmling\'s skin is really soft."};
descriptions["20760"]={cn:"一条小青石龙，能敏捷地穿越小山丘， 步态轻盈地随着毁灭之风翱翔。",en:"A little Lazurite Dragon, capable of flying over small cliffs, swept by the Stasified winds."};
descriptions["20761"]={cn:"这张床在某些地方有点潮湿，但还是能很好地小憩一下的。",en:"This bed is a little damp in certain areas, but it\'s perfectly good for a little nap."};
descriptions["20762"]={cn:"一个由触手伸展形成的桌子，在上面玩你的游戏吧。",en:"A tentacly sprawling table for all your games."};
descriptions["20763"]={cn:"中间的这跟触手十分强壮，你甚至可以把厚重的衣服挂在这柜子里。",en:"You can easily suspend heavy clothing in this cupboard using the very strong central tentacle."};
descriptions["20764"]={cn:"一个柜子，你的任何小秘密都可以深藏柜中。",en:"A dresser where every little secret has its place."};
descriptions["20765"]={cn:"这扇屏风能保护你不受诱惑。",en:"This screen is perfect for protecting your being from temptation."};
descriptions["20766"]={cn:"一种只在夜间枝繁叶茂的植物。",en:"A plant which flourishes in the evening."};
descriptions["20767"]={cn:"三两密友，一盘桌游。",en:"A little game to play with close friends."};
descriptions["20768"]={cn:"小小祭坛，用于颂扬奥古大鱿的崇高品德。",en:"A small altar, suitable for honoring the virtues of the god Oktapodas."};
descriptions["20769"]={cn:"这枚美丽的深蓝色龙蛋是幸福与宁静的象征。一条幼龙行将出世。",en:"This beautiful, deep blue Dofus is a symbol of happiness and serenity. A baby dragon is about to be born."};
descriptions["20770"]={cn:"你把幼龙孵化后的空蛋壳留了下来以纪念它的诞生。",en:"You\'ve kept your little Wyrmling\'s empty shell as a souvenir of its birth."};
descriptions["20771"]={cn:"“奥古蛰伏处，神尊梦眠静候时，寂海残庙中”",en:"\"In his home, the Sunken Temple, the god dreams and waits\""};
descriptions["20772"]={cn:"多么可爱又柔软的幼龙毛绒玩具，轻拿轻放，可别摔了它！",en:"A beautiful soft, stuffed toy of your dearest Wyrmling. Be careful, it\'s not a meter in length!"};
descriptions["20773"]={cn:"奇妙米米的著名召唤兽，现已加入庇护袋豪华套餐！",en:"Mimi the Marvelous\'s famous Summons, finally in your Haven Bag!"};
descriptions["20774"]={cn:"一个奇妙米米的填充人偶，如果你想她了就看看这个人偶吧。",en:"A stuffed effigy of Michelene Tordsabots, just in case you missed her."};
descriptions["20775"]={cn:"美丽记忆，永久珍藏。",en:"A nice trophy for your personal collection."};
descriptions["20776"]={cn:"美丽记忆，永久珍藏。",en:"A nice trophy for your personal collection."};
descriptions["20777"]={cn:"美丽记忆，永久珍藏。",en:"A nice trophy for your personal collection."};
descriptions["20778"]={cn:"美丽记忆，永久珍藏。",en:"A nice trophy for your personal collection."};
descriptions["20779"]={cn:"你可以尽情拥抱这只小小怪鱿。",en:"You can embrace this Nekark at the whim of your desires."};
descriptions["20780"]={cn:"这个火盆来自奥古大鱿的海底神庙。",en:"This brazier comes straight from Oktapodas\'s Sunken Temple."};
descriptions["20781"]={cn:"这件装饰品很正宗也很脆弱，毕竟已经在海底神庙放了那么久了。",en:"This decoration is authentic and very fragile, given the years spent in the Sunken Temple."};
descriptions["20782"]={cn:"完成顽强英雄试炼的人的称号奖励！",en:"A title for those who have passed the tests of the Tenacious Hero."};
descriptions["20783"]={cn:"战胜可怕怪鱿的人的称号奖励！",en:"A title for those who have faced the terrible Nekark!"};
descriptions["20784"]={cn:"这支笛子能鼓励你的霍比龙飞跃小悬崖！",en:"This Ocarina lets you encourage the Dragominus to overcome small cliffs!"};
descriptions["20785"]={cn:"把巨大的克殊鲁油炸后，小巧可口的食物。\n给亚龙及Gardon吃的食物",en:"A small, but very tasty, giant Koutoulou doughnut.\nThis powder is used as food for the Dragominus and Gradon mounts."};
descriptions["20786"]={cn:"\"我爱自己！\"",en:"\"I love myself!\""};
descriptions["20787"]={cn:"\"用你的脑袋\"",en:"\"Use your head\""};
descriptions["20788"]={cn:"\"我不会放弃我的朋友！\"",en:"\"I won\'t abandon my friends!\""};
descriptions["20789"]={cn:"一场意外会让你陷入非常非常糟糕的情绪。",en:"An incident could put you in a very, very bad mood."};
descriptions["20790"]={cn:"这柄鱼叉对抗怪鱿触手效果拔群，但是叉个小鱼小虾却完全叉不上来。",en:"This harpoon is very effective against Nekark tentacles, but it won\'t be much use against crefishes, even immature ones."};
descriptions["20791"]={cn:"拧紧鹦鹉螺号螺栓的最佳道具非它莫属。可惜它不属于你...",en:"There\'s nothing better to tighten the Nemotilus\'s bolts. Too bad it doesn\'t belong to you..."};
descriptions["20792"]={cn:"使用这个将激活或取消终结者。这不是一件消耗品。它会随机激活一种终结者。",en:"Using this will activate or deactivate the Finisher. The item is not consumed. Random selection among all active Finishers."};
descriptions["20802"]={cn:"保证是低卡路里和无脂肪的牛奶。最好倒着喝！",en:"This Mimilk comes with a low calorie and fat free guarantee. Best drunk upside down!"};
descriptions["20803"]={cn:"穿着这件野牛风的士兵服，你向敌人摆出冲锋的架势他们就会吓尿裤子！",en:"With this soldier costume which has a buffalo look about it, your opponents soil themselves if you look as if you\'re going to charge at them!"};
descriptions["20804"]={cn:"这件套装能让你看起来像炎龙伊格尼迈卡，知名的火元素龙。虽然是迷你型...",en:"This costume will make you look like Ignemikhal, the famous Fire Elemental Dragon, but in miniature form..."};
descriptions["20805"]={cn:"对想cosplay成彩虹小马的人来说再完美不过的一套套装。",en:"A perfect costume for all those who have always dreamed of turning into a rainbow Unikron pony..."};
descriptions["20806"]={cn:"教会你使用“吐火”表情。",en:"This scroll will teach you the \"Breathe Fire\" emote."};
descriptions["20807"]={cn:"教会你使用“做就是了！”表情。",en:"This scroll will teach you the \"But Do It\" emote."};
descriptions["20808"]={cn:"妥善保管一万年的话，你就有机会见证真龙诞生的瞬间！",en:"To be kept safe and warm for an eternity or so, this will give you the chance to see a dragon hatch - a real one!"};
descriptions["20809"]={cn:"这种广受好评的逗逗龙命名自黑龙古迦洛哈格，尽管外观相似却没有黑龙的强大力量。但愿它光凭外观就能吓倒你的敌人！",en:"This highly prized species of Dragoone draws its name from its resemblance to Grougaloragran, but not its powers. Let\'s hope it\'s enough to impress your opponents!"};
descriptions["20810"]={cn:"这件古遗物是一个上古能量之源，用于启动机关。",en:"This ancient relic is an ancient energy source used to activate mechanisms."};
descriptions["20811"]={cn:"一条小霍比龙，能敏捷地穿越小山丘， 步态轻盈地随着毁灭之风翱翔。",en:"A little Lazurite Dragon, capable of flying over small cliffs, swept by the Stasified winds."};
descriptions["20812"]={cn:"一条小霍比龙，能敏捷地穿越小山丘， 步态轻盈地随着毁灭之风翱翔。",en:"A little Lazurite Dragon, capable of flying over small cliffs, swept by the Stasified winds."};
descriptions["20813"]={cn:"一条小霍比龙，能敏捷地穿越小山丘， 步态轻盈地随着毁灭之风翱翔。",en:"A little Lazurite Dragon, capable of flying over small cliffs, swept by the Stasified winds."};
descriptions["20815"]={cn:"你需要在神庙用它和青石龙蛋进行交换后将其孵化。",en:"You need to hatch this item by exchanging it for the Lazurite Dofus in the temple."};
descriptions["20819"]={cn:"5年时光来之不易，且行且珍惜！ 充满惊奇的冒险仍在继续...",en:"5 years isn\'t nothing, and it should be celebrated! The adventure continues and is full of surprises..."};
descriptions["20820"]={cn:"使用这个道具变得疯狂！（不会消耗）",en:"When used, this item activates or deactivates the change of running. The item is not consumed."};
descriptions["20821"]={cn:"教会你使用“匪国伞”表情。",en:"This scroll will teach you the \"Riktus Clan Umbrella\" emote."};
descriptions["20822"]={cn:"教会你使用“插上你公会的旗帜”表情。",en:"This scroll will teach you the \"Plants Your Guild\'s Flag\" emote."};
descriptions["20824"]={cn:"这个魔药可以提升你所有生活技能的制造、种植、及收获速度的100% (x2) 一小时。",en:"This potion increases the speed of crafting, planting and harvesting in all your professions by 100% (x2) for one hour."};
descriptions["20825"]={cn:"这该是 JIF 还是 GIF？",en:"Should it be pronounced JIF or GIF?"};
descriptions["20826"]={cn:"这套非常特殊的坐骑装饰能使绵球先锋装扮起来更像一只圣诞绵球。",en:"A Gobball War Chief skin in Kwismas colors."};
descriptions["20827"]={cn:"这个卷轴教会你使用“我是一块小饼干”表情。",en:"This scroll will teach you the \"I Am a Li\'l Biscuit\" emote."};
descriptions["20830"]={cn:"美丽记忆，永久珍藏。",en:"A nice trophy for your personal collection."};
descriptions["20831"]={cn:"美丽记忆，永久珍藏。",en:"A nice trophy for your personal collection."};
descriptions["20834"]={cn:"使用时可以让你在跑步和走路之间切换，这个物品不会被消耗。",en:"When used, this item activates or deactivates the change of running. The item is not consumed."};
descriptions["20835"]={cn:"使用这个道具变得疯狂！（不会消耗）",en:"When used, this item activates or deactivates the change of running. The item is not consumed."};
descriptions["20913"]={cn:"顶着如此称号，你必气定神闲！",en:"With a title like that, you won\'t miss a breath!"};
descriptions["20914"]={cn:"哆哆哆，冷到能把布丁冻成冰棍！",en:"Brrr, it\'s cold enough to freeze a Puddly!"};
descriptions["20916"]={cn:"一条战甲霍比龙，能敏捷地穿越小山丘， 步态轻盈地随着毁灭之风翱翔。",en:"A little Gradon, capable of flying over small cliffs, swept by the Stasified winds."};
