descriptions["20918"]={cn:"一条战甲霍比龙，能敏捷地穿越小山丘， 步态轻盈地随着毁灭之风翱翔。",en:"A little Gradon, capable of flying over small cliffs, swept by the Stasified winds."};
descriptions["20919"]={cn:"一条战甲霍比龙，能敏捷地穿越小山丘， 步态轻盈地随着毁灭之风翱翔。",en:"A little Gradon, capable of flying over small cliffs, swept by the Stasified winds."};
descriptions["20921"]={cn:"这个霍比龙的造型是沙子的配色。",en:"This Gradon skin is the color of sand."};
descriptions["20922"]={cn:"教会你使用“气功波”表情。",en:"This scroll will teach you the \"Kameha\" emote."};
descriptions["20926"]={cn:"为了庆祝叶落归根！来杯啤酒，不，来坛好酒！",en:"For a return to your roots! Root beer, or even the real stuff!"};
descriptions["20927"]={cn:"一个蛋壳形状的戒指。",en:"An egg-squisite ring."};
descriptions["20928"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。\n打开它只需要两秒！",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with the mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["20929"]={cn:"这个胸甲是一个想要坚不可摧的人制作的，除了里面。",en:"This breastplate was created by someone who wanted to be impenetrable, except on the inside."};
descriptions["20930"]={cn:"这种头饰的魅力不在于它让你看起来秃顶，而在于你接受了它。",en:"This headgear\'s charm lies not in the fact that it makes you look bald, but more in the fact that you accept it."};
descriptions["20931"]={cn:"尽管经过了几个世纪，这些祖传的鞋子并没有失去它们的主要用途：它们仍然是很好的烧烤签子。",en:"Despite the centuries, these ancestral boots haven\'t lost their main use: they\'re still great barbecue skewers."};
descriptions["20932"]={cn:"蛋龙每年都要举行一次造型比赛。最丑的衣服就这样被抛弃了，这就是为什么你最后穿着这件披风的原因...",en:"Dreggons come together once a year for a style contest. The most ugly attire is thus abandoned, which explains how you ended up wearing this cloak..."};
descriptions["20933"]={cn:"许多学识渊博的人试图制造一种像蛋龙壳一样坚固的材料，但从这个盾牌来看，并没有多少人成功。",en:"Many knowledgeable people have tried to craft a material that is as solid as Dreggon Shells, but without much success, judging by this shield."};
descriptions["20934"]={cn:"不，不是那种可以放进口袋的腰带，而是有很多口袋的腰带。这样子更有用。",en:"No, not as in a belt that you can fit in your pocket, but a belt with many pockets. That\'s far more useful."};
descriptions["20935"]={cn:"早餐，有人要吗？",en:"Breakfast, anyone?"};
descriptions["20936"]={cn:"都在食谱里！",en:"It\'s all in the cooking!"};
descriptions["20937"]={cn:"这顶帽子是袖珍型的。它体积更小，几秒钟就可以折叠起来：所有的设计都很便于携带。",en:"This headgear is a pocket model. It\'s smaller and folds up in just a few seconds: all of it has been designed so it\'s easy to transport."};
descriptions["20938"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。\n打开它只需要两秒！",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with the mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["20939"]={cn:"不足以让你将双脚塞进去。",en:"The Foot Ring isn\'t big enough for you to put both feet in it."};
descriptions["20940"]={cn:"无法保证有跟浓稠度一样高的坚硬度。",en:"Its consistency will not reassure you as to its solidity."};
descriptions["20941"]={cn:"穿起来很自在。",en:"You\'ll feel easy wearing these."};
descriptions["20942"]={cn:"胸甲内里的薄膜使得穿戴起来非常舒适。一天结束后，你会感觉像个新生儿一样干净。",en:"The inner membrane of this improvised breastplate makes it very comfortable for its wearer. You\'ll feel as clean as a newborn child at the end of the day."};
descriptions["20943"]={cn:"吽曾是个伟大的蛋龙首领。至少我们是这么认为的。",en:"Goh was a great leader among the Dreggons. That\'s what we think, at least."};
descriptions["20944"]={cn:"这是一条无力的双头蛋龙能够穿戴的配件。",en:"This is the kind of accessory an ineffective Dregger can wear."};
descriptions["20945"]={cn:"双头蛋龙的目的就是让你戴上这只戒指。知道这件事后，你确定还想戴上它吗？",en:"The Dregger\'s aim is to slip it on your finger. Knowing this, are you still so sure you want to wear it?"};
descriptions["20946"]={cn:"学习是一生的事。你最好尽快开始，因为“一生”实际上很长的。",en:"Learning is a lifelong experience. You\'re best starting as early as possible, because \"lifelong\" is indeed quite long."};
descriptions["20947"]={cn:"皮匠们总是对如何将物品用于奇怪用途方面特别有天分...",en:"Leather Dealers have always been talented when it comes to finding unorthodox uses for items..."};
descriptions["20948"]={cn:"这双靴子属于一只会吃蛋龙孩子的食人魔。",en:"These boots belonged to an Ogre who ate Dreggon children."};
descriptions["20949"]={cn:"力量、恐惧、敬畏...那些望向你的人，被你激起了许多东西。",en:"Power, terror, fear... You inspire many things in those who lay their eyes upon you."};
descriptions["20950"]={cn:"有如恒星爆炸般明亮。",en:"As bright as an exploding star."};
descriptions["20951"]={cn:"能用来对抗敌人或喝些有益健康的汤。",en:"You can use it to fight off you enemies or to eat some wholesome soup."};
descriptions["20952"]={cn:"那些比任何人早一步知道情报的人，有着重大的责任。别跟人说这条腰带的功能！",en:"A great responsibility weighs on those who have information before anyone else. Don\'t tell anyone what this belt does!"};
descriptions["20953"]={cn:"这条来自上古时代的护符在战斗中很有帮助，能够保护你免于失去斗志并直取要害。",en:"This amulet from the Dofus Era will make all the difference in combat by protecting you from a lack of ambition. And hits to the throat."};
descriptions["20954"]={cn:"它真的挺坚固。",en:"It really is quite strong."};
descriptions["20955"]={cn:"摩擦左肩会出现邪恶的精灵永恒地折磨你；摩擦右肩会出现善良的精灵实现你最大的愿望。还是左右反过来才是对的？",en:"Rub the left epaulette and an evil genie will torment you for all eternity; rub the right one and a good genie will make your greatest wish come true. Or is it the other way around?"};
descriptions["20956"]={cn:"能防御精神攻击。但这功能没什么用，没人想知道会去戴这顶头盔的人脑袋里在想什么。",en:"This protects you from mental attacks. But that\'s not useful. No one wants to know what\'s inside the head of anyone who\'d wear this headgear."};
descriptions["20957"]={cn:"得到这东西的战斗之艰辛，堪称你活到现在之最：活到现在。",en:"You got this during the most difficult fight of your life: your life."};
descriptions["20958"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few drops should suffice."};
descriptions["20959"]={cn:"这种非常坚固的鳞片被用来制作许多令人难以置信的物品。刷子、袋子、窗帘、木制品...",en:"This very solid scale is used to make many fabulous items. Brushes, bags, curtains, woodwork..."};
descriptions["20960"]={cn:"这是用来做帽架的。",en:"This is used to make hat stands."};
descriptions["20961"]={cn:"这种坚不可摧的蛋壳最终被证实并不是那么一回事。",en:"This reputedly unbreakable shell ended up proving to be the exact opposite."};
descriptions["20962"]={cn:"这是一颗尚未孵化的蛋，被残忍地从它的父母那里夺走。",en:"This is an egg that hasn\'t yet hatched. It was cruelly snatched away from its parents."};
descriptions["20963"]={cn:"尽管外表和香气感觉都可以食用，但这实际上是一种有毒的资源，它已经结束了许多冒险家的生命。",en:"Albeit of edible appearance and aroma, this is actually a poisoned resource that has ended numerous adventurers\' lives."};
descriptions["20966"]={cn:"伴着三叶草啤酒品尝这些美味的小饼干，最能带出丰富的口味和激爽的口感。随心所欲的吃吧。\n(持续1场战斗)",en:"These divine little biscuits go hand in hand with Clover Root Beer to really bring out those precious flavors and zests. Consume liberally. \n(Lasts 1 combat)"};
descriptions["20967"]={cn:"和你的朋友们整夜狂欢吧！",en:"This will keep your friends on their toes all night long!"};
descriptions["20968"]={cn:"可以在下列兑奖机使用此奖章兑换奖励：冷山、食人草原、哞哞地下城。",en:"Use the following machines to exchange your tokens for fantastic rewards: Crackler, Plant, Moogrr."};
descriptions["20969"]={cn:"这是...旋鸟婚礼的...好日子！你看起来比拉森努斯·华莱士更像摇滚明星！",en:"It\'s a... nice day for a... Whirly weddiiing! YEAH! You look more rock \'n\' roll than Larsenus Wallace!"};
descriptions["20970"]={cn:"谁想得到帝王旋鸟竟然喜欢珠宝首饰？当他在时髦排队上翩翩起舞的时候，戒指会闪闪发光。",en:"Who knew the head of the Whirlies was such a fan of jewelry?! This one glints subtly as he twirls in and out of rooms at swanky parties."};
descriptions["20971"]={cn:"再也不会因为穿得不正式被拒之门外。来吧，来喱维萨的时髦夜总会吧！",en:"Goodbye, being turned away at the door for informal footwear; hello, Bilbiza\'s trendiest clubs!"};
descriptions["20972"]={cn:"亮丽光鲜，吸引着人群目光，使你成为舞会上最受瞩目的美女。穿上闪亮的胸衣和金闪闪的项链，你看上去比圣诞树还漂亮！",en:"This cloak sparkles and shines all over to make you the most questionably dressed belle at the ball.  Grab a shiny breastplate and a golden amulet and you\'ll look even better than the Kwismas tree!"};
descriptions["20973"]={cn:"现在你终于做好准备像个真正的士兵一样打仗了。好了，向前爬...呃，我是说向前冲！",en:"You\'re finally ready to fight like a true soldier. Crawl Out! Erm, I mean FALL out!"};
descriptions["20974"]={cn:"外硬内柔，战斗时柔软的内衬会不断挠你的脚趾。",en:"Hard on the outside, their inside is lightly quilted with a soft lining that will tickle your toes while you\'re kicking butt."};
descriptions["20975"]={cn:"为什么不穿上和朋友们跳支舞呢？",en:"Why not take these on a whirl with your friends?"};
descriptions["20976"]={cn:"由旋鸟背部的皮毛制成，松软有弹性，保护你在正面对敌时，不受伤害。",en:"This breastplate, which is supposed to protect the front of your body, was, in fact, made with a Whirly\'s backside, which is softer and more elastic.\n"};
descriptions["20977"]={cn:"一旦插入受害者的体内，就不停旋转，能削下大片的肉。",en:"Once they\'ve been planted into their victim, these daggers continue to turn, just to carve as much meat as possible off their prey."};
descriptions["20978"]={cn:"外观十分漂亮的卡牌，闪着诡异的光芒。你情不自禁地想打斗地主。",en:"These cards look so pretty and whimsical when you drop them from a height that some people refuse to play anything but 52-Card Pickup with them."};
descriptions["20979"]={cn:"在乌贼岛上很受欢迎，那里四季炎热如夏。在日光浴爱好者面前走过，他们会永生难忘。",en:"This cloak is most welcome on places like Calamar Island, where the heat is unbearable for much of the year. Twirl gently near the sunbathers and they\'ll be eternally grateful."};
descriptions["20980"]={cn:"皇家的旋转舞才够劲！",en:"When the whirl is not enough... try going Royal."};
descriptions["20981"]={cn:"轻便和舒适的鞋子，让穿着他们的人能在冰上来去自如。",en:"These shoes are so light and comfortable that the participants of Prancing on Ice swear by them!"};
descriptions["20982"]={cn:"显然，这枚戒指的拥有者将可以从树上优雅地转到地上。它曾经属于一个刺客，但是戒指的力量让他疯狂了。",en:"Apparently, anyone who puts this ring on will have the magical power to twirl gracefully down from a tree to the ground. It used to belong to a Sram, but its powers left him in pieces."};
descriptions["20983"]={cn:"让你一整天看起来潇洒倜傥...像个旋鸟一样翩翩起舞吧！",en:"These epaulettes will keep you cool all day long - and let you play at being a helicopter! Wheee!"};
descriptions["20984"]={cn:"这个护符让你看起来像是旋鸟们的国王。",en:"A lovely amulet to add to your collection!"};
descriptions["20986"]={cn:"它会让你想睡觉...",en:"It makes you feel like sleeping..."};
descriptions["20987"]={cn:"终于，十年的苦功能派上用处了！",en:"Finally, ten years of baton twirling classes will pay off!"};
descriptions["20988"]={cn:"闪耀着神秘的红光，从时光漩涡迷雾中，唤醒强大力量。",en:"When used, this wand glimmers and glows with powers called forth from the swirling mists of time!"};
descriptions["20989"]={cn:"腰上佩戴此件腰带不仅可以让你随意的扭动，还可以使你整夜都没有束缚感！我可真是个了不起的发明家。",en:"With this belt around your hips, you can twist and shout all night long! Why not change your name to Russell? Go wild!"};
descriptions["20990"]={cn:"这个头盔的内部都被旋鸟种子覆盖，这样可以保持这个你的头部一直处于舒适的状态。",en:"This helmet is covered in Whirly Seeds, which helps it fit snugly around heads of all shapes and sizes."};
descriptions["20991"]={cn:"如此美妙的时光！",en:"Such a whirly good time!"};
descriptions["20992"]={cn:"这副护肩属于一个奸商：旋鸟卡波尼。",en:"These epaulettes belonged to a rogue trader: Whirly Capone."};
descriptions["20993"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with the mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["20994"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with the mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["20995"]={cn:"谁是首领？",en:"Who\'s the boss?!"};
descriptions["20996"]={cn:"把戒指戴在不同的手指上会有不同的效果。这些细节都写在一份神秘的古代手稿中，但不幸的是，它似乎无法翻译。",en:"Putting this ring on different fingers gets different results. The details were all written down in a mysterious ancient manuscript, but unfortunately, it seems to be untranslatable."};
descriptions["20997"]={cn:"一只死去的旋鸟和一只死去的豆芙很相似，有时候很容易混淆。",en:"It is disturbing how similar a dead Whirly and a dead Tofu are!"};
descriptions["20998"]={cn:"总有捣蛋鬼喜欢戴上它来吓唬其他游泳的人。真好玩...当然，当他被海怪当做是活鱼的时候就不好玩了。",en:"Some practical jokers stick this thing on their back to scare the bathers. What fun... until they get mistaken for helpless fish by the local sea monster, that is."};
descriptions["20999"]={cn:"它看起来像个婴儿漏斗，但是实际上它要比外表看起来有用的多。",en:"It looks like a baby space hopper, but in reality, it\'s used for much more serious things."};
descriptions["21001"]={cn:"可以在下列兑奖机使用此奖章兑换奖励：蟹皇领地、椰树林、蚌蚌地下城、鲨鱼地下城、兽人地下城、野兽巢穴、黑珍珠码头。",en:"Use the following machines to exchange your tokens for fantastic rewards: Cwab, Kokoko, Mollusky, Selachii, Bwork, Wild Gobball, Dark Hurl."};
descriptions["21002"]={cn:"可以在下列兑奖机使用此奖章兑换奖励：咕哩泥塘、废弃鸵鸟城堡、滋滋宫殿、满月祭坛、盘丝洞、卡波 - 洞穴、鸦人大酋长神庙、鼠群之墓。",en:"Use the following machines to exchange your tokens for fantastic rewards: Blibli, Strich, Mushdskito, Boowolf, Arachnee, Crobak, Raskaw, Ratatomb."};
descriptions["21003"]={cn:"可以在下列兑奖机使用此奖章兑换奖励：骸骨都市、矿洞骸骨、废弃虫洞、巨魔学院、修道院深处、迷荫地、瓦格纳城堡、珍蚌地下城、斯雷克地下城。",en:"Use the following machines to exchange your tokens for fantastic rewards: Chafer, Mine Chafer, Scaraleaf, Trool, Monk, Zoogeyman, Vampyro, Mussly Hammam, Schnek."};
descriptions["21004"]={cn:"可以在下列兑奖机使用此奖章兑换奖励：土匪据点、劲舞秀场、果冻地下城、寒冰咕哩地下城、吉狼狼的巢穴、寂静之殿。",en:"Use the following machines to exchange your tokens for fantastic rewards: Riktus, Bilbiboy, Jelly, Brrrbli, Boohemoth, Whisperer."};
descriptions["21005"]={cn:"可以在下列兑奖机使用此奖章兑换奖励：布丁地下城、迷之渔场、哈根达兹要塞、大使之翼、冰冻之塔、掌仙人地下城、旋路车站、磨魂窟。",en:"Use the following machines to exchange your tokens for fantastic rewards: Puddly, Snapper, Polar Crackler, Northern Chafer, Mecha, Castuc, Whirly, Tormentor."};
descriptions["21006"]={cn:"可以在下列兑奖机使用此奖章兑换奖励：黑暗树精、隐藏的学院、黑暗孢子地下城、魔眼窟、黑疯兔地下城、福狸王的宫殿、疯兔地下城、松露庄园。",en:"Use the following machines to exchange your tokens for fantastic rewards: Dark Treechnid, Huppermage, Blackspore, Flaxhid, Black Wabbit, Lenald, Wabbit, Drheller."};
descriptions["21007"]={cn:"可以在下列兑奖机使用此奖章兑换奖励：软妮、邪恶葡萄园、废弃的胡萝卜储藏室、兔皇帝的城堡、斯拉姆、埃努卓、茎怪。",en:"Use the following machines to exchange your tokens for fantastic rewards: Blop, Viticultist, Zwombbit, Wabbit Guawd, Srambad, Enurado, Plantala."};
descriptions["21008"]={cn:"可以在下列兑奖机使用此奖章兑换奖励：土匪老巢、盗贼、基地号飞艇、石笋旅店、械卡工厂、机械迷城、卡利老巢。",en:"Use the following machines to exchange your tokens for fantastic rewards: Elite Riktus, Rogue, Hoodlum, Stalagmote, Mecha Factory, Ow El, Kali\'s Lair."};
descriptions["21010"]={cn:"可以在下列兑奖机使用此奖章兑换奖励：獾兽巢穴、熔岩火山、蛋龙、天气球、祸豹、潘达拉幽灵、鸮鸟。",en:"Use the following machines to exchange your tokens for fantastic rewards: Badgerox, Dor\'Mor, Dreggon, Ethernal, Blightopard, Pandala Ghost, Bubourg."};
