descriptions["21115"]={cn:"胶水是物品制作中的理想原料。 可以通过完成36-50级的地图限时任务获得。",en:"Souper-Glou is the ideal ingredient to assemble your items. You can get it as a reward for the level 36 to 50 Environmental Quests."};
descriptions["21116"]={cn:"胶水是物品制作中的理想原料。 可以通过完成51-65级的地图限时任务获得。",en:"Souper-Glou is the ideal ingredient to assemble your items. You can get it as a reward for the level 51 to 65 Environmental Quests."};
descriptions["21117"]={cn:"胶水是物品制作中的理想原料。 可以通过完成66-80级的地图限时任务获得。",en:"Souper-Glou is the ideal ingredient to assemble your items. You can get it as a reward for the level 66 to 80 Environmental Quests."};
descriptions["21118"]={cn:"胶水是物品制作中的理想原料。 可以通过完成81-95级的地图限时任务获得。",en:"Souper-Glou is the ideal ingredient to assemble your items. You can get it as a reward for the level 81 to 95 Environmental Quests."};
descriptions["21119"]={cn:"胶水是物品制作中的理想原料。 可以通过完成96-110级的地图限时任务获得。",en:"Souper-Glou is the ideal ingredient to assemble your items. You can get it as a reward for the level 96 to 110 Environmental Quests."};
descriptions["21120"]={cn:"胶水是物品制作中的理想原料。 可以通过完成111-125级的地图限时任务获得。",en:"Souper-Glou is the ideal ingredient to assemble your items. You can get it as a reward for the level 111 to 125 Environmental Quests."};
descriptions["21121"]={cn:"胶水是物品制作中的理想原料。 可以通过完成126-140级的地图限时任务获得。",en:"Souper-Glou is the ideal ingredient to assemble your items. You can get it as a reward for the level 126 to 140 Environmental Quests."};
descriptions["21122"]={cn:"胶水是物品制作中的理想原料。 可以通过完成141-155级的地图限时任务获得。",en:"Souper-Glou is the ideal ingredient to assemble your items. You can get it as a reward for the level 141 to 155 Environmental Quests."};
descriptions["21123"]={cn:"胶水是物品制作中的理想原料。 可以通过完成156-170级的地图限时任务获得。",en:"Souper-Glou is the ideal ingredient to assemble your items. You can get it as a reward for the level 156 to 170 Environmental Quests."};
descriptions["21124"]={cn:"胶水是物品制作中的理想原料。 可以通过完成171-185级的地图限时任务获得。",en:"Souper-Glou is the ideal ingredient to assemble your items. You can get it as a reward for the level 171 to 185 Environmental Quests."};
descriptions["21125"]={cn:"胶水是物品制作中的理想原料。 可以通过完成186-200级的地图限时任务获得。",en:"Souper-Glou is the ideal ingredient to assemble your items. You can get it as a reward for the level 186 to 200 Environmental Quests."};
descriptions["21126"]={cn:"鲨鱼牙齿项链实在太过时了...\n今年，请选择蚌壳项链！",en:"Shark tooth necklaces are so yesterday...\nThis year, choose the Mussamulet!"};
descriptions["21127"]={cn:"真可惜，这件胸甲居然没有更大号的。否则你就可以整天呆在里面，把自己蜷成一团，一整天在海滩上吹风，无忧无虑。",en:"Too bad this breastplate isn\'t bigger, or else you could curl up inside it and chill on the beach all day, safe from harm."};
descriptions["21128"]={cn:"你会想念穿着这双靴子去钓鱼的日子的！",en:"The boots of choice for budding marine biologists, these Waders will help you blend in when standing in rock pools the World over."};
descriptions["21129"]={cn:"在任何灾难中都能让你安然无恙，肌肉看起来坚实有力。。",en:"These epaulettes will keep you safe in any clamity, and they make your mussels look huge!"};
descriptions["21130"]={cn:"在海滩边上捡起一块漂亮的贝壳，在上面挖两个洞，大功告成。游客们最好骗了！",en:"Choose a pretty shell off the beach, drill two holes in it, and you\'ve got yourself a product. Tourists love this stuff!"};
descriptions["21131"]={cn:"撬开蚌壳的好工具，不伤手。",en:"Very useful for opening mumussels without hurting yourself."};
descriptions["21132"]={cn:"不要把戒指和炸爱鱿圈搞混了。你的牙齿会遭殃的。",en:"Make sure you don\'t mix this ring up with a Kralove donut. Your teeth will be sorely disappointed."};
descriptions["21133"]={cn:"吉他手丰古斯·杨的最爱。拉森努斯·华莱士从他那里偷得了这件披风，希望能从中吸取一些摇滚明星的精髓。",en:"This cloak was a firm favorite of guitarist Fungus Young\'s, before Larsenus Wallace stole it from him in the hopes of absorbing some of its rockstar essence."};
descriptions["21134"]={cn:"等等！你得知道一旦戴上就取不下来了。除非你想把所有的头发都扯下来。",en:"WAIT! Before you put this hat on, know that it\'s forever. Unless, of course, you\'re interested in ripping all your hair out trying to get it off."};
descriptions["21135"]={cn:"软软的胸甲，一下子就黏上了皮肤。据说会造成65%的穿戴者的过敏反应！这就是为什么它只卖半价的原因...",en:"This gloopy breastplate sticks fast to your skin and is known to give 65% of wearers allergic reactions! So that\'s why it was half price..."};
descriptions["21136"]={cn:"戴着这对护肩，你看起来像个有钱人。",en:"With these sailor-made epaulettes on your shoulders, you look very whelk-to-do indeed."};
descriptions["21137"]={cn:"别打死结。你可不想把刺激性的东西挂在你的腰间。",en:"Make sure you don\'t stick the two ends of this belt together. You don\'t want irritant bits near your... irritable bits."};
descriptions["21138"]={cn:"多触手的护符，能治愈部分病痛，例如晕船以及海鲜中毒！",en:"This tentacular amulet can cure certain illnesses, most notably sea sickness and sea food poisoning!"};
descriptions["21139"]={cn:"噗噗...它在水里...",en:"Plop... it\'s in the water..."};
descriptions["21140"]={cn:"柔中带刺，成双成对。有没有联想到什么东西？",en:"They\'re soft yet scratchy and there are two of them. Remind you of anything?"};
descriptions["21141"]={cn:"注意：接触敏感皮肤易导致皮疹，穿戴前请使用防护霜。",en:"Warning: Contact with sensitive skins may cause hives. You should apply cream before use."};
descriptions["21142"]={cn:"梦想成真！你终于可以变身章鱼了！",en:"Have you always dreamed of looking like an octopus? Now you can!"};
descriptions["21143"]={cn:"如果你不知道这把弓的使用方法，你可以把它当成法杖来用。只有骑士才不知道怎么用这把弓。",en:"If you don\'t know how to use this bow, you can always pretend it\'s a staff. Then again, only a real Iop doesn\'t know how to use a bow."};
descriptions["21144"]={cn:"一旦你成功用这把锤子击败了敌人，那么千万不要再用第二次！里面的恶魔会苏醒过来，更加疯狂邪恶。",en:"If you manage to knock your target out with this hammer, whatever you do, don\'t hit it again! It might just come back to life, madder and badder than ever!"};
descriptions["21145"]={cn:"哦哦，快来看这只可爱的戒指，上面还有个小天线...噗呲呲呲！",en:"Awww, just look at this adorable little ring, with its little antennae and... BZZZT!"};
descriptions["21146"]={cn:"即使房子着火了，Vertigo也会告诉你一切都很好。这种软体动物是完美的，它可以泰然自若地面对任何情况。",en:"Even in a house on fire, Vertigo will tell you that everything\'s fine. This Mollusky\'s a consummate one, who\'s ready to take on any situation with indifference."};
descriptions["21147"]={cn:"这个头盔很舒服，但是它会时不时地释放一点电击，只是为了让你保持警惕。",en:"This helmet is comfortable enough, but it has a tendency to let out a little electric shock from time to time, just to keep you on your toes."};
descriptions["21148"]={cn:"你见过这东西吗？它们在水里泡了很久！它们依然很没用，但是看起来不错，不是吗？",en:"Oh man, have you seen these things? They swell up in the water! I mean, that doesn\'t make them any more useful, but still! Cool, right?"};
descriptions["21149"]={cn:"一码通用的腰带。菊芋片吃多了可以系起来防止肚子饱胀。",en:"A belt that really is one-size-fits-all. Pretty useful if you\'ve gone overboard on the Artichoke Chips!"};
descriptions["21150"]={cn:"它会把你给它的爱都还给你...咸咸的口水喷涌而出。",en:"It will give back all the love you give it... in spurts of salty drool."};
descriptions["21151"]={cn:"由早已过时的鲨鱼鳍制成。穿上去萨弗基亚的海滩边吓人吧！",en:"These epaulettes were fashioned out of fins removed from shark carcasses. Slap them on your shoulders and get ready to terrorize Sufokia!"};
descriptions["21152"]={cn:"为了你自己着想，把上面的牙齿磨得钝一些。",en:"Leave the teeth included with this helmet as blunt as possible. Your head will thank you for it."};
descriptions["21153"]={cn:"你可以在水里穿这件披风来吓唬观光客！",en:"With this cape, you can play the old \'shark in the water\' trick on the poor, unsuspecting tourists!"};
descriptions["21154"]={cn:"穿着这双靴子，你看起来像个正牌海中刑警！",en:"With these shoes on your feet, you\'ll look like an authentic crimebuster of the sea!"};
descriptions["21155"]={cn:"小小鲨鱼，大大牙齿。",en:"Tiny little shark, big sharp teeth."};
descriptions["21156"]={cn:"记住：时刻倾听自己的内心！",en:"Just remember: always let your Conchus be your guide!"};
descriptions["21157"]={cn:"散发着起码五十种不同的血腥味。比如草莓味的治愈者鲜血以及木糖醇口味的植物术士鲜血，当然还有少许熊猫武僧的酒味鲜血。",en:"There must be at least fifty shades of blood on this cloak, from fruity Eniripsa blood to wood-scented Sadida blood, not forgetting a few healthy spatters of milky Pandawa blood."};
descriptions["21158"]={cn:"头盔上的白牙依旧十分锋利，所以要么脱下来，否则你得当心你的鼻子了！",en:"This hat\'s teeth are still very sharp, so file \'em down or watch your nose!"};
descriptions["21159"]={cn:"就像任何自尊自爱、怕水的鲨鱼一样，制作这些护肩所用的布料是 100% 防雨的。",en:"Just like any self-respecting, aquaphobic Selachii, the fabric used to make these epaulettes is 100% rainproof."};
descriptions["21160"]={cn:"在撒克雅女神的婚礼上，这枚戒指从此戴在了她的手上。很显然，这样的戒指她都收到过几十枚了，不过这份心意毕竟给到了。",en:"This is the ring the goddess Sacrier was offered for her hand in marriage. Obviously, she already had dozens like it, but it\'s the thought that counts."};
descriptions["21161"]={cn:"很锋利的腰带，不要怀疑，流下来的血是你的。快叫救护车！",en:"If that belt is anywhere near as sharp as it looks, some of the blood dripping off it is definitely yours. Call a medic!"};
descriptions["21162"]={cn:"隐匿身形，发出可怕的声音，侦测树后的昆虫和蜘蛛...",en:"These boots are the bees\' knees at detecting insects and Arachnees hiding amongst the trees... being invisible... and making creepy clicking noises. Brrr!"};
descriptions["21163"]={cn:"和鲨鱼牙齿一样锋利。",en:"As sharp as a sharp shark tooth."};
descriptions["21164"]={cn:"在高博球风靡一时之前，流行用鲨鱼斧狠狠地刺破骸骨的头。这项运动已经从布拉克玛的官方体育联盟中删除。",en:"Before Gobbowl was all the rage, whacking a Chafer\'s head with a Squalachii was a hit. This sport has since been removed from the official league of sports in Brakmar."};
descriptions["21165"]={cn:"鲨鱼牙齿以能够锯穿所有类型的木材而闻名。有了这把剑，你将成为一名优秀的伐木战士！",en:"Selachii Teeth are well-known for being able to saw through all types of wood. With this sword, you\'ll be a fighter-slash-lumberjack par excellence!"};
descriptions["21166"]={cn:"不放心自己辛辛苦苦挣来的卡玛的人有福了。有了此盾，他们大可安心。",en:"This is great for those who want to look after their hard-earned kamas. Finally, a shield made for the well-off!"};
descriptions["21167"]={cn:"可爱的名字，配上可怕的肩甲。啊呜！",en:"A cutesy-wutesy name for a pair of cutesy-wutesy... enormous... intimidating epaulettes. Gulp!"};
descriptions["21168"]={cn:"你也许不知道鲨鱼也有肌肉，现在你知道了。觉得怎么样？它们可是世界上最坚硬的胸肌！",en:"You may not have known that they had pecs, but now that you do know, do you not agree that they must be among the toughest in the World?"};
descriptions["21169"]={cn:"仍然滴着受难者的鲜血。",en:"The messiest cards ever. Period."};
descriptions["21170"]={cn:"多亏了里面厚实的海藻，没有一颗子弹能穿透它。",en:"Thanksh to all the sheaweed inshide thish shield, not a shingle bullet will shucsheed in reaching you."};
descriptions["21171"]={cn:"别妄想戴着这枚戒指去蒸汽海岸。如果被那里的生物闻到血腥味，它们才不管究竟是你还是你的戒指发出的。",en:"Don\'t even think about getting near the Steamulating Shore with this ring. If they smell fresh blood, they won\'t care whether it\'s yours or your ring\'s."};
descriptions["21172"]={cn:"仍然滴着鲜血。穆斯堂上校在锅炉房犯下鱼叉谋杀案的时候，就穿着这件披风。",en:"There\'s fresh blood still dripping from this cloak. Colonel Mustang was wearing it when he committed a murder in the boiler room with the harpoon. That game didn\'t last long."};
descriptions["21173"]={cn:"你必须把这副血迹斑斑的护肩脱掉，现在！立刻！马上！",en:"You just want to take these Blood-Stained Epaulettes off, now!"};
descriptions["21174"]={cn:"你腿上怎么有条纹？哦...对不起...仅仅是你的血而已。没事没事，我什么都没看到。",en:"Are those pin-striped legs you\'ve got there? Oh... Sorry... It\'s just the blood from your belt. That\'s embarrassing."};
descriptions["21175"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few drops should suffice."};
descriptions["21176"]={cn:"幸福膏，幸福膏！吃过都说好，一口百病消，两口万事顺，三口赛神仙！",en:"Euphoric resin! If you eat it, it\'ll really make your head spin!"};
descriptions["21177"]={cn:"丢掉礼节，大快朵颐！",en:"Manners cost nothing..."};
descriptions["21178"]={cn:"幸运向你微笑！",en:"Fortune is smiling upon you!"};
descriptions["21179"]={cn:"爱向你微笑！",en:"Love is smiling upon you!"};
descriptions["21180"]={cn:"好帽知时节，当春乃发生！",en:"It\'s spring! It\'s sprung!"};
descriptions["21181"]={cn:"为第一个五年欢呼，然后带着这个沃土颜色的袋子准备好迎接下一个五年吧！",en:"Celebrate the first five years and get ready for the next five with this Haven Bag Kit, in the colors of WAKFU!"};
descriptions["21182"]={cn:"现在，你觉得打开庇护袋就像是打开一盒巧克力。",en:"From now on, you\'ll get the feeling that opening your Haven Bag is like opening a box of chocolates."};
descriptions["21183"]={cn:"这个垫子是给坚持到最后的玩家准备的，谢谢你们的陪伴！",en:"This cushion is only offered to players who stay to the end. Thanks for your loyalty!"};
descriptions["21184"]={cn:"这套时装不能让你液化变成布丁，但是能让你免于晒伤和饥渴。",en:"This costume doesn\'t give you the power of liquefying yourself, but it protects you from both sun and thirst."};
descriptions["21185"]={cn:"你做梦都做了五年了，现在还不想醒来！除非你在一张如此可爱的床上。",en:"You\'ve been dreaming for five years, and you don\'t want to wake up just yet! Unless it\'s in a lovely bed such as this one."};
descriptions["21186"]={cn:"为了庆祝这五年的美好，这里有一张可爱的餐桌，可以吃一些 WAKFU，更多 WAKFU，甚至更多 WAKFU！请享用！",en:"To celebrate these five wonderful years, here\'s a lovely table to eat some WAKFU, more WAKFU, and even more WAKFU! Enjoy your meal!"};
descriptions["21187"]={cn:"在过去的五年中，你总共收藏了多少披风、头盔、套装和时装？这个柜子里能装得下所有的东西吗？",en:"How many capes, hats, sets and costumes have you been able to accumulate over the last five years? Could this cupboard contain all of them?"};
descriptions["21188"]={cn:"五年的小饰品，啾啾羽毛、绵球羊毛、喵喵猫毛...这个梳妆台唤起了许多回忆。",en:"Five years of trinkets, piwi feathers, gobball wool, bow meow hairs... This dresser brings back many memories."};
descriptions["21189"]={cn:"不要隐藏你对沃土的爱；表达你的感受，感谢这个玩了五年游戏！",en:"Don\'t hide your love for WAKFU; express yourself, thanks to this screen commemorating five years of the game!"};
descriptions["21190"]={cn:"这种植物花了五年的时间才长出来；谁知道再过五年它会增长多少呢？",en:"This plant has taken five years to grow; who knows how much it\'ll have grown in another five years?"};
descriptions["21191"]={cn:"经过五年的冒险之后，沃土团队的全体成员都非常高兴。这多亏了你，你是其中的一部分。",en:"The whole WAKFU team is on cloud nine after five years of adventure. And seeing as that\'s kind of thanks to you, here\'s a piece of it."};
descriptions["21192"]={cn:"不要等五年才展示这个旗帜，现在就展示吧！",en:"Don\'t wait five years to display this standard; show it off now!"};
descriptions["21193"]={cn:"在这个祭坛前祈祷会给沃土开发者带来五年的幸福和平安。不管你做什么，都不要把火熄灭：那样会延迟更新。",en:"Praying before this altar brings well-being and safety to the WAKFU developers for five years. And whatever you do, don\'t blow the flame out: that\'ll delay updates."};
descriptions["21194"]={cn:"小心别走在这块地毯上；你不会想要毁掉这五年史诗般的冒险！",en:"Take care not to walk on this carpet; you wouldn\'t want to stamp on five years of epic adventures!"};
descriptions["21195"]={cn:"乌黑的、令人作呕的血。说真的，你打算用它做什么？",en:"Black, nauseating blood. Really, what are you going to do with that?"};
descriptions["21196"]={cn:"凝结的血液沾满了锁链...",en:"Chains covered in coagulated blood..."};
descriptions["21197"]={cn:"从受害者身上撕下的一簇红头发。",en:"A tuft of red hair torn from a victim."};
descriptions["21198"]={cn:"一块破的、打过补丁的布。",en:"A piece of worn and patched fabric."};
descriptions["21199"]={cn:"这个小瓶里有从经验丰富的牧民那里提取的浓缩血液！几滴就足够了。",en:"This vial contains the concentrated blood taken from an experienced trapper! A few drops should suffice."};
descriptions["21200"]={cn:"狂战士纹身用的墨水...有的人说这是魔法。",en:"Ink for Sacriers\' tattoos... Some say that it\'s magic."};
descriptions["21201"]={cn:"这个卷轴会教你如何表达“干杯！”",en:"This scroll will teach you the \"Cheers!\" emote."};
descriptions["21202"]={cn:"幸运猫忌讳使用这把斧头，因为他们讨厌血脉枯竭。",en:"Ecaflips avoid this axe because they hate running out of veins."};
descriptions["21203"]={cn:"创口、骨裂、骨折...这条围巾可用于治疗各种类型的创伤。",en:"Wounds, fractures, broken bones... this scarf is useful against all types of ills."};
descriptions["21204"]={cn:"波拉诺的病好了以后，她很会挖苦人，而且很精通挖苦人的艺术。",en:"When Borano healed, she was sarcastic, and was rather well-versed in the caustic arts."};
descriptions["21205"]={cn:"一件斗篷，为那些喜欢血流不止的人打造。",en:"A cape for those who enjoy spilling blood and can\'t stop."};
descriptions["21206"]={cn:"当骑士 Marc Daul 误闯军械库，大叫“旅馆老板，标准间！”时，他拿起了这根棒子，因为缺少他梦寐以求的呵口可乐。",en:"When the Iop Marc Daul cried \"Innkeeper, a double!\" when mistakenly entering an armory, he took this stick for lack of the Cacta-Cola that he so desired."};
descriptions["21207"]={cn:"我的身体，裹着受伤的绷带，\n我的伤口，被安全地包裹着，\n在风中自由地飘动，\n我表现出疯狂，而你将会哭泣！\n所以我悄然地离去，像一个可怕的畜生，\n我的手上有你的血，我的脚上有你的鞋！\n“憎恨”的波否，一名狂战士以及闲暇时的吟游诗人。",en:"My body is covered in Wounded Straps,\nMy injuries, though, are safely wrapped,\nIn the wind they are freely flowing,\nI show my madness, and you\'ll be crying!\nAnd so I leave, like a horrid brute,\nOn my hands your blood, on my feet your boots!\n— Polver \"The Hate\", Sacrier and bard in his spare time."};
descriptions["21208"]={cn:"让你内心的愤怒沸腾吧！",en:"Let the rage inside you boil!"};
descriptions["21209"]={cn:"对于那些缺少一些牙齿的人来说，是一枚完美的戒指。",en:"A ring that\'s perfect for those who are missing a few toothy-pegs."};
descriptions["21210"]={cn:"愤怒、狂乱、嗜血...那就是这枚戒指带给你的...",en:"Fury, frenzy, thirst for blood... That\'s what this ring will bring you..."};
descriptions["21211"]={cn:"这是给爱咬指甲的人戴的戒指。更重要的是，它的味道更好。",en:"A ring to nibble on for those who bite their nails. What\'s more, it tastes better."};
descriptions["21212"]={cn:"有了这个护肩，没人敢去找你的麻烦。因为他们担心会气得你满脸通红。",en:"With these epaulettes, no one will dare go looking for trouble with you, out of fear that you\'ll become red with rage."};
descriptions["21213"]={cn:"这个护符配上一颗红宝石，看起来像一只充满愤怒的红眼，正盯着你。",en:"Set with a ruby, this amulet looks like a red eye full of anger, staring at you."};
descriptions["21214"]={cn:"这条充满魔力的腰带使佩戴者嗜血成性。",en:"This belt, imbued with magic, makes its wearer surprisingly bloodthirsty."};
descriptions["21215"]={cn:"这条腰带太紧了。忒紧了。",en:"This belt is tight. Far too tight."};
descriptions["21216"]={cn:"为普通血统狂战士准备的高级披风。",en:"A high-ranking cape for an ordinarily-blooded Sacrier."};
descriptions["21217"]={cn:"这件披风和“太空外套”携手而来，“太空外套”是一件著名的铠甲，和它的制作者Cap\'tain Eddy一起由火箭发射升空。",en:"This cape goes hand in hand with the \"Space Tunic\", a famous coat of mail that was launched on a rocket along with its creator, the equally famous Cap\'tain Eddy."};
descriptions["21218"]={cn:"你从来没有因为一想到吹干头发就吓得尖叫过吗？",en:"Have you never screamed with fright at the thought of a blow-dry?"};
descriptions["21219"]={cn:"所以你可以完全疯了...",en:"So you can go completely nuts..."};
descriptions["21220"]={cn:"一个完美的头盔助你做特技动作向前翻滚和降落在你的敌人旁边而不伤到你自己。",en:"A perfect helmet for doing acrobatic forward rolls and landing next to your enemy without injuring yourself."};
descriptions["21221"]={cn:"你身上有个伤口？穿上这件沾着酸的外套，过两天你就没事了，除了几处表面的烧伤。",en:"A gash on your torso? Put on this coat with hints of acid for two days and you\'re sorted, minus a few superficial burns."};
descriptions["21222"]={cn:"你应该时刻警惕那些除了一块血迹斑斑的布外没有任何盔甲的战士。",en:"You should always be wary of fighters who have nothing in terms of armor but a simple, bloodied piece of fabric."};
descriptions["21223"]={cn:"要在战斗前呐喊，你需要大量的吸气。如果你没有足够的肺活量，这件胸甲至少可以达成共振。",en:"To scream before a battle, you need a lot of puff. If you don\'t have enough, this armor may at least be useful as a resonance chamber."};
descriptions["21224"]={cn:"这双靴子会使你撞到任何移动的东西。",en:"These boots make you want to hit everything that moves."};
descriptions["21225"]={cn:"最亲爱的人...",en:"Dearest..."};
descriptions["21226"]={cn:"想走在最伟大的狂战士道路上，你需要先弄脏你的鞋子。",en:"To walk the path of the greatest Sacriers, you need to get your shoes dirty first."};
descriptions["21227"]={cn:"Redith Splaf沾满鲜血，但没有受到任何怀疑，由于这把被诅咒的匕首，她透过玫瑰色的眼镜看到了生命。",en:"Red with blood, but clean of any suspicion, Redith Splaf saw life through rose-tinted glasses thanks to this cursed dagger."};
descriptions["21228"]={cn:"有可能会伤到你的头骨。但是你是从斯雷克那里得到的...你还能指望些什么？",en:"It might crush your skull, but you got it from the Schneks - what did you expect?"};
descriptions["21229"]={cn:"吸水性强，紧紧贴住你的皮肤。",en:"This spongy cloak will stick to your skin like proverbial feces to a blanket."};
descriptions["21230"]={cn:"弹力极强的手镯，适合任何手腕...甚至是你的，肥仔！",en:"This elastic bracelet will fit around any wrist... even yours!"};
descriptions["21231"]={cn:"斯雷克护膝让你远离受伤烦恼...湿软的内衬，足以抵抗任何冲击。",en:"You needn\'t worry about getting attacked with these knee pads on - they\'re squidgy enough to cushion the blow."};
descriptions["21232"]={cn:"能承受一切赘肉！",en:"This belt will hold in all that excess weight!"};
descriptions["21233"]={cn:"伸缩自如，适用于任何一根手指。",en:"This ring is so elastic it will adapt its size to any finger you choose to wear it on."};
descriptions["21234"]={cn:"即使你失去了一点，它还会再长回来。",en:"Even if you lose a bit of it, it\'ll grow back."};
descriptions["21235"]={cn:"这件诱人的背心将保护你不摩擦地面。",en:"This seductive top will protect you from rubbing against the ground."};
descriptions["21236"]={cn:"他们曾经是得体的穿着。",en:"They were once worn gracefully."};
descriptions["21237"]={cn:"它让你保持温暖，让你在走动时更加优雅。",en:"It keeps you warm and makes you much more elegant when you move."};
descriptions["21238"]={cn:"没必要再战斗了！",en:"No need to fight any longer!"};
descriptions["21239"]={cn:"这是给你已经满溢的收藏品增添的另一个护符。",en:"Another good luck charm for your already overflowing collection."};
descriptions["21240"]={cn:"跑起来，别用走的！",en:"Run, not gait!"};
descriptions["21241"]={cn:"戴上这个肩甲，释放你桀骜不驯的灵魂。",en:"You\'ll feel like a rebellious soul in these epaulettes."};
descriptions["21242"]={cn:"真是骇人听闻...",en:"It really is appalling..."};
descriptions["21243"]={cn:"我们已经不在萨弗基亚了。在这里，你不能穿着拖鞋骑龙鸟。",en:"We\'re not in Sufokia any more. Here, you don\'t ride your Dragoturkeys while wearing thongs."};
descriptions["21244"]={cn:"它有点旧了，但仍然很有趣。",en:"It\'s a bit old, but is still interesting indeed."};
descriptions["21245"]={cn:"你该休息下，为什么不在盾牌后面躲一会儿...？",en:"You deserve a break, so why not just hide behind this schnexy schield...?"};
descriptions["21246"]={cn:"现在你戴着手铐。但这并不意味着你不能用你的脚战斗...或者你的头。",en:"Now you\'re handcuffed. But that doesn\'t mean you can\'t still fight with your feet... or your head."};
descriptions["21247"]={cn:"甩出这条鞭子，敌人像蠕虫一样退却。",en:"Whip this out and watch your adversaries squirm!"};
descriptions["21248"]={cn:"保护你的头部免受坠落之物的伤害。你可不知道铁砧会掉在哪里！",en:"This hat will protect your head from any falling objects whilst you\'re here. You never know when an anvil might fall out of nowhere!"};
descriptions["21249"]={cn:"这件外套很好看，其实并不会提供多好的防护。那么，对于野外冒险来说是好看还是防护更重要呢...？",en:"This jacket won\'t protect you too well, but it certainly looks good. Now, which is more important for wild adventures...?"};
descriptions["21250"]={cn:"靴子的特制内衬，提供良好的缓冲性能，脚底再也不会起泡。",en:"These boots have special insoles that prevent rubbing and blisters - your feet are sure to be as pleased as punch... ur... kick."};
descriptions["21251"]={cn:"它不能阻止你的死亡，但至少能让你体面地屈服！",en:"It won\'t stop you from dying, but at least you\'ll succumb in style!"};
descriptions["21252"]={cn:"幸运猫忌讳使用这把斧头，因为他们讨厌血脉枯竭。",en:"Ecaflips avoid this axe because they hate running out of veins."};
descriptions["21253"]={cn:"创口、骨裂、骨折...这条围巾可用于治疗各种类型的创伤。",en:"Wounds, fractures, broken bones... this scarf is useful against all types of ills."};
descriptions["21254"]={cn:"波拉诺的病好了以后，她很会挖苦人，而且很精通挖苦人的艺术。",en:"When Borano healed, she was sarcastic, and was rather well-versed in the caustic arts."};
descriptions["21255"]={cn:"一件斗篷，为那些喜欢血流不止的人打造。",en:"A cape for those who enjoy spilling blood and can\'t stop."};
descriptions["21256"]={cn:"让你内心的愤怒沸腾吧！",en:"Let the rage inside you boil!"};
