descriptions["21321"]={cn:"添加到庇护袋的制造室或者庇护领地里，你就能用该设备完成 0 - 40 级畜牧配方。",en:"Once added to the Crafting Room of your Haven Bag or to your Haven World, you can use this equipment to make level 0 to 40 recipes for the Trapper profession."};
descriptions["21322"]={cn:"添加到庇护袋的制造室或者庇护领地里，你就能用该设备完成 0 - 40 级伐木工配方。",en:"Once added to the Crafting Room of your Haven Bag or to your Haven World, you can use this equipment to make level 0 to 40 recipes for the Lumberjack profession."};
descriptions["21323"]={cn:"添加到庇护袋的制造室或者庇护领地里，你就能用该设备完成 0 - 40 级厨师配方。",en:"Once added to the Crafting Room of your Haven Bag or to your Haven World, you can use this equipment to make level 0 to 40 recipes for the Chef profession."};
descriptions["21324"]={cn:"添加到庇护袋的制造室或者庇护领地里，你就能用该设备完成 0 - 40 级珠宝师配方。",en:"Once added to the Crafting Room of your Haven Bag or to your Haven World, you can use this equipment to make level 0 to 40 recipes for the Jeweler profession."};
descriptions["21325"]={cn:"添加到庇护袋的制造室或者庇护领地里，你就能用该设备完成 0 - 40 级工匠配方。",en:"Once added to the Crafting Room of your Haven Bag or to your Haven World, you can use this equipment to make level 0 to 40 recipes for the Handyman profession."};
descriptions["21326"]={cn:"添放到庇护袋的制作室或庇护领地里，你可以使用此设备制作 0 到 40 的武器。",en:"By adding it to the Crafting Room of your Haven Bag or to your Haven World, you can use this equipment to make recipes of level 0 to 40 for the Weapons Master profession."};
descriptions["21327"]={cn:"添加到庇护袋的制造室或者庇护领地里，你就能用该设备完成 0 - 40 级皮匠配方。",en:"Once added to the Crafting Room of your Haven Bag or to your Haven World, you can use this equipment to make level 0 to 40 recipes for the Leather Dealer profession."};
descriptions["21328"]={cn:"有可能会伤到你的头骨。但是你是从斯雷克那里得到的...你还能指望些什么？",en:"It might crush your skull, but you got it from the Schneks - what did you expect?"};
descriptions["21329"]={cn:"吸水性强，紧紧贴住你的皮肤。",en:"This spongy cloak will stick to your skin like proverbial feces to a blanket."};
descriptions["21330"]={cn:"弹力极强的手镯，适合任何手腕...甚至是你的，肥仔！",en:"This elastic bracelet will fit around any wrist... even yours!"};
descriptions["21331"]={cn:"能承受一切赘肉！",en:"This belt will hold in all that excess weight!"};
descriptions["21332"]={cn:"有可能会伤到你的头骨。但是你是从斯雷克那里得到的...你还能指望些什么？",en:"It might crush your skull, but you got it from the Schneks - what did you expect?"};
descriptions["21333"]={cn:"吸水性强，紧紧贴住你的皮肤。",en:"This spongy cloak will stick to your skin like proverbial feces to a blanket."};
descriptions["21334"]={cn:"弹力极强的手镯，适合任何手腕...甚至是你的，肥仔！",en:"This elastic bracelet will fit around any wrist... even yours!"};
descriptions["21335"]={cn:"斯雷克护膝让你远离受伤烦恼...湿软的内衬，足以抵抗任何冲击。",en:"You needn\'t worry about getting attacked with these knee pads on - they\'re squidgy enough to cushion the blow."};
descriptions["21336"]={cn:"能承受一切赘肉！",en:"This belt will hold in all that excess weight!"};
descriptions["21337"]={cn:"伸缩自如，适用于任何一根手指。",en:"This ring is so elastic it will adapt its size to any finger you choose to wear it on."};
descriptions["21338"]={cn:"即使你失去了一点，它还会再长回来。",en:"Even if you lose a bit of it, it\'ll grow back."};
descriptions["21339"]={cn:"这件诱人的背心将保护你不摩擦地面。",en:"This seductive top will protect you from rubbing against the ground."};
descriptions["21340"]={cn:"他们曾经是得体的穿着。",en:"They were once worn gracefully."};
descriptions["21341"]={cn:"它让你保持温暖，让你在走动时更加优雅。",en:"It keeps you warm and makes you much more elegant when you move."};
descriptions["21342"]={cn:"跑起来，别用走的！",en:"Run, not gait!"};
descriptions["21343"]={cn:"真是骇人听闻...",en:"It really is appalling..."};
descriptions["21344"]={cn:"它们很旧了，而且已经有一股陈旧的味道。",en:"They\'re very worn, and already have a cheesy scent."};
descriptions["21345"]={cn:"它有点旧了，但仍然很有趣。",en:"It\'s a bit old, but is still interesting indeed."};
descriptions["21370"]={cn:"收集 100 块碎片，合成血淋腰带。",en:"Collect 100 of these fragments to create Wounded Straps."};
descriptions["21371"]={cn:"只要摆放的位置正确，就能喷射出跨越天际的彩虹。",en:"Position this shard correctly to create a double rainbow, all the way across the sky."};
descriptions["21372"]={cn:"空荡荡的贝壳，有股蚌类的腥味。",en:"An empty shell which smells of old mussels. Nice..."};
descriptions["21374"]={cn:"油炸特别好吃。如果要凑齐一顿大餐的量可能有点难...你必须击败一群蚌蚌！",en:"Mussels like this one are delicious with fries. Good luck getting enough of them for a meal though - you\'ll have to battle a whole horde of Molluskies!"};
descriptions["21375"]={cn:"有没有人跟你说过你有一颗热爱鱿鱼的心？",en:"Has anyone ever told you that you have the heart of a Kralove?"};
descriptions["21376"]={cn:"从大王爱鱿身上移除之后，这只角就学乖了...然而，你得记住，永远不要相信睡眠中的蚌蚌。",en:"Once removed from the Kralaboss, this horn should behave itself... Still, as they say, never trust a sleeping Mollusky."};
descriptions["21377"]={cn:"鲨鱼牙齿项链实在太过时了...\n今年，请选择蚌壳项链！",en:"Shark tooth necklaces are so yesterday...\nThis year, choose the Mussamulet!"};
descriptions["21378"]={cn:"真可惜，这件胸甲居然没有更大号的。否则你就可以整天呆在里面，把自己蜷成一团，一整天在海滩上吹风，无忧无虑。",en:"Too bad this breastplate isn\'t bigger, or else you could curl up inside it and chill on the beach all day, safe from harm."};
descriptions["21379"]={cn:"你会想念穿着这双靴子去钓鱼的日子的！",en:"The boots of choice for budding marine biologists, these Waders will help you blend in when standing in rock pools the World over."};
descriptions["21380"]={cn:"在海滩边上捡起一块漂亮的贝壳，在上面挖两个洞，大功告成。游客们最好骗了！",en:"Choose a pretty shell off the beach, drill two holes in it, and you\'ve got yourself a product. Tourists love this stuff!"};
descriptions["21381"]={cn:"在海滩边上捡起一块漂亮的贝壳，在上面挖两个洞，大功告成。游客们最好骗了！",en:"Choose a pretty shell off the beach, drill two holes in it, and you\'ve got yourself a product. Tourists love this stuff!"};
descriptions["21382"]={cn:"鲨鱼牙齿项链实在太过时了...\n今年，请选择蚌壳项链！",en:"Shark tooth necklaces are so yesterday...\nThis year, choose the Mussamulet!"};
descriptions["21383"]={cn:"真可惜，这件胸甲居然没有更大号的。否则你就可以整天呆在里面，把自己蜷成一团，一整天在海滩上吹风，无忧无虑。",en:"Too bad this breastplate isn\'t bigger, or else you could curl up inside it and chill on the beach all day, safe from harm."};
descriptions["21384"]={cn:"你会想念穿着这双靴子去钓鱼的日子的！",en:"The boots of choice for budding marine biologists, these Waders will help you blend in when standing in rock pools the World over."};
descriptions["21385"]={cn:"在任何灾难中都能让你安然无恙，肌肉看起来坚实有力。。",en:"These epaulettes will keep you safe in any clamity, and they make your mussels look huge!"};
descriptions["21386"]={cn:"撬开蚌壳的好工具，不伤手。",en:"Very useful for opening mumussels without hurting yourself."};
descriptions["21387"]={cn:"多触手的护符，能治愈部分病痛，例如晕船以及海鲜中毒！",en:"This tentacular amulet can cure certain illnesses, most notably sea sickness and sea food poisoning!"};
descriptions["21388"]={cn:"噗噗...它在水里...",en:"Plop... it\'s in the water..."};
descriptions["21389"]={cn:"等等！你得知道一旦戴上就取不下来了。除非你想把所有的头发都扯下来。",en:"WAIT! Before you put this hat on, know that it\'s forever. Unless, of course, you\'re interested in ripping all your hair out trying to get it off."};
descriptions["21390"]={cn:"软软的胸甲，一下子就黏上了皮肤。据说会造成65%的穿戴者的过敏反应！这就是为什么它只卖半价的原因...",en:"This gloopy breastplate sticks fast to your skin and is known to give 65% of wearers allergic reactions! So that\'s why it was half price..."};
descriptions["21391"]={cn:"戴着这对护肩，你看起来像个有钱人。",en:"With these sailor-made epaulettes on your shoulders, you look very whelk-to-do indeed."};
descriptions["21392"]={cn:"柔中带刺，成双成对。有没有联想到什么东西？",en:"They\'re soft yet scratchy and there are two of them. Remind you of anything?"};
descriptions["21393"]={cn:"注意：接触敏感皮肤易导致皮疹，穿戴前请使用防护霜。",en:"Warning: Contact with sensitive skins may cause hives. You should apply cream before use."};
descriptions["21394"]={cn:"梦想成真！你终于可以变身章鱼了！",en:"Have you always dreamed of looking like an octopus? Now you can!"};
descriptions["21423"]={cn:"自从鲨鱼牙齿加入热门电影《大白鲨》中客串以来，它就不停地吹嘘，并且哼唱主题曲。",en:"Ever since this Selachii Tooth landed a cameo in the cult film Jaw, it won\'t stop bragging about it and humming the theme tune."};
descriptions["21424"]={cn:"鲨鱼的皮肤以非常厚而闻名。不幸的是，它也很油、很重、很滑。",en:"Selachii Skin is known for being very thick. Unfortunately, it\'s also very greasy, very heavy and very slippery."};
descriptions["21425"]={cn:"调查结果正在核实中，我们需要知道这血是鲨鱼的还是受害者身上的。",en:"Tests are underway to investigate whether this blood came from a Selachii or from one of its victims."};
descriptions["21426"]={cn:"专为健康的口腔提供。",en:"For healthy jaws."};
descriptions["21427"]={cn:"你认为这是成为沙滩派对上“滑稽的家伙”的好方法；它所能做的只是在你最意想不到的时候关掉电灯开关。",en:"You thought this would be a great way to become \"the funny guy\" at beach parties; all it really does is turn off light switches when you\'re least expecting it."};
descriptions["21428"]={cn:"由早已过时的鲨鱼鳍制成。穿上去萨弗基亚的海滩边吓人吧！",en:"These epaulettes were fashioned out of fins removed from shark carcasses. Slap them on your shoulders and get ready to terrorize Sufokia!"};
descriptions["21429"]={cn:"为了你自己着想，把上面的牙齿磨得钝一些。",en:"Leave the teeth included with this helmet as blunt as possible. Your head will thank you for it."};
descriptions["21430"]={cn:"你可以在水里穿这件披风来吓唬观光客！",en:"With this cape, you can play the old \'shark in the water\' trick on the poor, unsuspecting tourists!"};
descriptions["21431"]={cn:"穿着这双靴子，你看起来像个正牌海中刑警！",en:"With these shoes on your feet, you\'ll look like an authentic crimebuster of the sea!"};
descriptions["21432"]={cn:"由早已过时的鲨鱼鳍制成。穿上去萨弗基亚的海滩边吓人吧！",en:"These epaulettes were fashioned out of fins removed from shark carcasses. Slap them on your shoulders and get ready to terrorize Sufokia!"};
descriptions["21433"]={cn:"为了你自己着想，把上面的牙齿磨得钝一些。",en:"Leave the teeth included with this helmet as blunt as possible. Your head will thank you for it."};
descriptions["21434"]={cn:"你可以在水里穿这件披风来吓唬观光客！",en:"With this cape, you can play the old \'shark in the water\' trick on the poor, unsuspecting tourists!"};
descriptions["21435"]={cn:"小小鲨鱼，大大牙齿。",en:"Tiny little shark, big sharp teeth."};
descriptions["21436"]={cn:"穿着这双靴子，你看起来像个正牌海中刑警！",en:"With these shoes on your feet, you\'ll look like an authentic crimebuster of the sea!"};
descriptions["21437"]={cn:"记住：时刻倾听自己的内心！",en:"Just remember: always let your Conchus be your guide!"};
descriptions["21438"]={cn:"和鲨鱼牙齿一样锋利。",en:"As sharp as a sharp shark tooth."};
descriptions["21439"]={cn:"在高博球风靡一时之前，流行用鲨鱼斧狠狠地刺破骸骨的头。这项运动已经从布拉克玛的官方体育联盟中删除。",en:"Before Gobbowl was all the rage, whacking a Chafer\'s head with a Squalachii was a hit. This sport has since been removed from the official league of sports in Brakmar."};
descriptions["21440"]={cn:"散发着起码五十种不同的血腥味。比如草莓味的治愈者鲜血以及木糖醇口味的植物术士鲜血，当然还有少许熊猫武僧的酒味鲜血。",en:"There must be at least fifty shades of blood on this cloak, from fruity Eniripsa blood to wood-scented Sadida blood, not forgetting a few healthy spatters of milky Pandawa blood."};
descriptions["21441"]={cn:"头盔上的白牙依旧十分锋利，所以要么脱下来，否则你得当心你的鼻子了！",en:"This hat\'s teeth are still very sharp, so file \'em down or watch your nose!"};
descriptions["21442"]={cn:"在撒克雅女神的婚礼上，这枚戒指从此戴在了她的手上。很显然，这样的戒指她都收到过几十枚了，不过这份心意毕竟给到了。",en:"This is the ring the goddess Sacrier was offered for her hand in marriage. Obviously, she already had dozens like it, but it\'s the thought that counts."};
descriptions["21443"]={cn:"鲨鱼牙齿以能够锯穿所有类型的木材而闻名。有了这把剑，你将成为一名优秀的伐木战士！XXX",en:"Selachii Teeth are well-known for being able to saw through all types of wood. With this sword, you\'ll be a fighter-slash-lumberjack par excellence!XXX"};
descriptions["21444"]={cn:"不放心自己辛辛苦苦挣来的卡玛的人有福了。有了此盾，他们大可安心。",en:"This is great for those who want to look after their hard-earned kamas. Finally, a shield made for the well-off!"};
descriptions["21445"]={cn:"可爱的名字，配上可怕的肩甲。啊呜！",en:"A cutesy-wutesy name for a pair of cutesy-wutesy... enormous... intimidating epaulettes. Gulp!"};
descriptions["21471"]={cn:"现在你终于做好准备像个真正的士兵一样打仗了。好了，向前爬...呃，我是说向前冲！",en:"You\'re finally ready to fight like a true soldier. Crawl Out! Erm, I mean FALL out!"};
descriptions["21472"]={cn:"外硬内柔，战斗时柔软的内衬会不断挠你的脚趾。",en:"Hard on the outside, their inside is lightly quilted with a soft lining that will tickle your toes while you\'re kicking butt."};
descriptions["21473"]={cn:"为什么不穿上和朋友们跳支舞呢？",en:"Why not take these on a whirl with your friends?"};
descriptions["21474"]={cn:"一旦插入受害者的体内，就不停旋转，能削下大片的肉。",en:"Once they\'ve been planted into their victim, these daggers continue to turn, just to carve as much meat as possible off their prey."};
descriptions["21475"]={cn:"现在你终于做好准备像个真正的士兵一样打仗了。好了，向前爬...呃，我是说向前冲！",en:"You\'re finally ready to fight like a true soldier. Crawl Out! Erm, I mean FALL out!"};
descriptions["21476"]={cn:"外硬内柔，战斗时柔软的内衬会不断挠你的脚趾。",en:"Hard on the outside, their inside is lightly quilted with a soft lining that will tickle your toes while you\'re kicking butt."};
descriptions["21477"]={cn:"为什么不穿上和朋友们跳支舞呢？",en:"Why not take these on a whirl with your friends?"};
descriptions["21478"]={cn:"由旋鸟背部的皮毛制成，松软有弹性，保护你在正面对敌时，不受伤害。",en:"This breastplate, which is supposed to protect the front of your body, was, in fact, made with a Whirly\'s backside, which is softer and more elastic.\n"};
descriptions["21479"]={cn:"一旦插入受害者的体内，就不停旋转，能削下大片的肉。",en:"Once they\'ve been planted into their victim, these daggers continue to turn, just to carve as much meat as possible off their prey."};
descriptions["21480"]={cn:"外观十分漂亮的卡牌，闪着诡异的光芒。你情不自禁地想打斗地主。",en:"These cards look so pretty and whimsical when you drop them from a height that some people refuse to play anything but 52-Card Pickup with them."};
descriptions["21482"]={cn:"它会让你想睡觉...",en:"It makes you feel like sleeping..."};
descriptions["21483"]={cn:"在乌贼岛上很受欢迎，那里四季炎热如夏。在日光浴爱好者面前走过，他们会永生难忘。",en:"This cloak is most welcome on places like Calamar Island, where the heat is unbearable for much of the year. Twirl gently near the sunbathers and they\'ll be eternally grateful."};
descriptions["21484"]={cn:"皇家的旋转舞才够劲！",en:"When the whirl is not enough... try going Royal."};
descriptions["21485"]={cn:"显然，这枚戒指的拥有者将可以从树上优雅地转到地上。它曾经属于一个刺客，但是戒指的力量让他疯狂了。",en:"Apparently, anyone who puts this ring on will have the magical power to twirl gracefully down from a tree to the ground. It used to belong to a Sram, but its powers left him in pieces."};
descriptions["21486"]={cn:"终于，十年的苦功能派上用处了！",en:"Finally, ten years of baton twirling classes will pay off!"};
descriptions["21487"]={cn:"闪耀着神秘的红光，从时光漩涡迷雾中，唤醒强大力量。",en:"When used, this wand glimmers and glows with powers called forth from the swirling mists of time!"};
descriptions["21488"]={cn:"腰上佩戴此件腰带不仅可以让你随意的扭动，还可以使你整夜都没有束缚感！我可真是个了不起的发明家。",en:"With this belt around your hips, you can twist and shout all night long! Why not change your name to Russell? Go wild!"};
descriptions["21489"]={cn:"再也不会因为穿得不正式被拒之门外。来吧，来喱维萨的时髦夜总会吧！",en:"Goodbye, being turned away at the door for informal footwear; hello, Bilbiza\'s trendiest clubs!"};
descriptions["21490"]={cn:"亮丽光鲜，吸引着人群目光，使你成为舞会上最受瞩目的美女。穿上闪亮的胸衣和金闪闪的项链，你看上去比圣诞树还漂亮！",en:"This cloak sparkles and shines all over to make you the most questionably dressed belle at the ball.  Grab a shiny breastplate and a golden amulet and you\'ll look even better than the Kwismas tree!"};
descriptions["21491"]={cn:"谁想得到帝王旋鸟竟然喜欢珠宝首饰？当他在时髦排队上翩翩起舞的时候，戒指会闪闪发光。",en:"Who knew the head of the Whirlies was such a fan of jewelry?! This one glints subtly as he twirls in and out of rooms at swanky parties."};
descriptions["21492"]={cn:"现在你终于做好准备像个真正的士兵一样打仗了。好了，向前爬...呃，我是说向前冲！",en:"You\'re finally ready to fight like a true soldier. Crawl Out! Erm, I mean FALL out!"};
