descriptions["21501"]={cn:"皇家的旋转舞才够劲！",en:"When the whirl is not enough... try going Royal."};
descriptions["21502"]={cn:"轻便和舒适的鞋子，让穿着他们的人能在冰上来去自如。",en:"These shoes are so light and comfortable that the participants of Prancing on Ice swear by them!"};
descriptions["21503"]={cn:"这个护符让你看起来像是旋鸟们的国王。",en:"A lovely amulet to add to your collection!"};
descriptions["21504"]={cn:"显然，这枚戒指的拥有者将可以从树上优雅地转到地上。它曾经属于一个刺客，但是戒指的力量让他疯狂了。",en:"Apparently, anyone who puts this ring on will have the magical power to twirl gracefully down from a tree to the ground. It used to belong to a Sram, but its powers left him in pieces."};
descriptions["21505"]={cn:"让你一整天看起来潇洒倜傥...像个旋鸟一样翩翩起舞吧！",en:"These epaulettes will keep you cool all day long - and let you play at being a helicopter! Wheee!"};
descriptions["21506"]={cn:"终于，十年的苦功能派上用处了！",en:"Finally, ten years of baton twirling classes will pay off!"};
descriptions["21507"]={cn:"闪耀着神秘的红光，从时光漩涡迷雾中，唤醒强大力量。",en:"When used, this wand glimmers and glows with powers called forth from the swirling mists of time!"};
descriptions["21508"]={cn:"腰上佩戴此件腰带不仅可以让你随意的扭动，还可以使你整夜都没有束缚感！我可真是个了不起的发明家。",en:"With this belt around your hips, you can twist and shout all night long! Why not change your name to Russell? Go wild!"};
descriptions["21509"]={cn:"这个头盔的内部都被旋鸟种子覆盖，这样可以保持这个你的头部一直处于舒适的状态。",en:"This helmet is covered in Whirly Seeds, which helps it fit snugly around heads of all shapes and sizes."};
descriptions["21510"]={cn:"如此美妙的时光！",en:"Such a whirly good time!"};
descriptions["21511"]={cn:"这副护肩属于一个奸商：旋鸟卡波尼。",en:"These epaulettes belonged to a rogue trader: Whirly Capone."};
descriptions["21512"]={cn:"这是...旋鸟婚礼的...好日子！你看起来比拉森努斯·华莱士更像摇滚明星！",en:"It\'s a... nice day for a... Whirly weddiiing! YEAH! You look more rock \'n\' roll than Larsenus Wallace!"};
descriptions["21513"]={cn:"这些烟火以爱和小爱心照亮了天空。",en:"These Fairyworks illuminate the sky with love and small hearts."};
descriptions["21515"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。\n打开它只需要两秒！",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with the mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["21516"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。\n打开它只需要两秒！",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with the mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["21518"]={cn:"坚硬有弹性，比一般的羊皮更优质！除非你和地穴兽一样眼瞎才分不清两者的优劣！",en:"Supple and strong, the leather is of much higher quality than ordinary Gobball leather! You\'d have to be as blind as a Drheller not to see the difference!"};
descriptions["21519"]={cn:"宝藏猎人用地穴兽獠牙来保护矿藏。如果你看到矿洞的墙壁上挂着这枚兽牙，这意味着：别碰我的矿！",en:"This tooth is used by Enutrofs to protect their mineral veins. If you see one hanging on the wall of a mine, the message is clear: no drilling!"};
descriptions["21520"]={cn:"地穴兽用手捂住它的心。等等...那不是你的心吗？",en:"This Drheller has his hand on his heart. Or...  is that your heart?"};
descriptions["21521"]={cn:"谁能想得到那个喜欢在自己的便便里打滚的动物能有这么丝滑的毛发？",en:"Who would have thought that the hair of an animal that likes to wallow in its own muck would be so silky?"};
descriptions["21522"]={cn:"能在任何物体上咬出一个洞来，无论是爱鱿肢体还是宝藏猎人的干巴脚板。",en:"This fang will pierce a neat hole in any kind of material, be it soft Kralove flesh or the dry skin on the bottom of an Enutrof\'s foot."};
descriptions["21523"]={cn:"由捣蛋兽皮制成，适用于任何地形。无论是布拉克玛的火山坡还是阿玛克纳的泥泞沼泽，都将如履平地。",en:"These boots were fashioned out of Rascal Leather and are hardy companions for all types of terrain, from Brakmar\'s volcanic slopes to the muddy marshlands of Amakna!"};
descriptions["21524"]={cn:"护肩上的鬃毛据说像地穴兽的牙齿一样锋利...又或者也许是犄角？我记不清了。反正它们都很锋利。",en:"The tufts on these epaulettes are supposed to represent the Drheller\'s sharp teeth... Or was it the horns? I can\'t remember. They hurt a lot, either way!"};
descriptions["21525"]={cn:"穿上它，四肢着地，像个真正的野兽一样攻击你的敌人。",en:"This cloak will make sure you stay stylish as you paw the ground and charge your enemy like a wild beast."};
descriptions["21526"]={cn:"捣蛋兽刚出生时戴过这只戒指。但是它现在戴不下了。它现在是个大家伙。",en:"Rascal used to wear this ring as a bracelet when he was a newborn. He can\'t wear it any more, though, can he? He\'s a big boy now! Who\'s a big, bad Drheller?"};
descriptions["21527"]={cn:"这个可爱的小皇冠非常适合你，就像地穴兽一样！",en:"This cute little crown fits you like a Drheller!"};
descriptions["21528"]={cn:"让你称心如意的披风。在地下岩石崩塌的时候可没什么用处。",en:"With this cloak, you can prospect to your heart\'s content. It won\'t save you from underground rockfalls, though."};
descriptions["21529"]={cn:"天啊！靴子上全是破洞！",en:"Golly galosh! These boots are just brimming with mischief!"};
descriptions["21530"]={cn:"这件肩甲几乎和地穴兽的獠牙一样结实！",en:"These epaulettes are almost as solid as Drheller Tusks!"};
descriptions["21531"]={cn:"腰带上的倒钩能阻止你的敌人逃跑。哇哈哈哈！",en:"This belt\'s hooks will prevent enemies from escaping your unending tomfoolery. Mwa ha ha ha!"};
descriptions["21532"]={cn:"由于无数次试图咬开宝箱大锁，大牙齿已经严重扭曲变形。",en:"This amulet is all twisted and mangled because it\'s been used so many times to force the locks on treasure chests."};
descriptions["21533"]={cn:"据说一只地穴兽和一只皮皮结合了，他们生出了长着尖刺的地穴兽...真爱无敌，不是吗？",en:"They say the spines on this breastplate can be explained by the fusion of a Drheller and a Prespic... Nothing can get in the way of true love, eh?"};
descriptions["21534"]={cn:"曾经属于胡埃·斯特劳德的地穴兽。如果贪婪的宝藏猎人看到你带着它，他会疯狂地用铲子追打你，让你好几周眼冒豆芙！",en:"This collar used to sit proudly around the neck of Ruel Stroud\'s Drheller. If the greedy Enutrof sees you with it, he\'ll hit you so hard with his shovel that you\'ll be seeing Tofus for weeks!"};
descriptions["21535"]={cn:"夕阳西下的时候，没有比弹一首曲子更惬意的了。",en:"At the crack of dawn, there\'s no sweeter sound than a lute ditty."};
descriptions["21536"]={cn:"为不安分的地穴兽专门设计。你需要做的只是把它戴上爱宠的脖子，然后就可以安心睡眠了！",en:"This amulet was designed with sleepless Drhellers in mind. All you had to do was slip it around your beloved pet\'s neck for a peaceful, refreshing night!"};
descriptions["21537"]={cn:"能静下来享受轻松真是太棒了。远离一切大大小小的战争战役的烦恼，安乐、平静、无忧无虑...",en:"Ah, it\'s nice to calm and relaxed, tucked away from all the wars and the bloody battles, happy, unruffled, inoffensive..."};
descriptions["21538"]={cn:"献给真正的领导者。裁判加油！",en:"A hammer for a real leader."};
descriptions["21539"]={cn:"制造这把武器的匠人工作了整整九天九夜将捣蛋兽牙改造成指针。",en:"The craftsman who made this weapon had to work for nine days and nine nights to turn a Rascal Tusk into a hand."};
descriptions["21540"]={cn:"拥有它的主人值得骄傲。原本指环是为捣蛋兽设计的，目的是为了防止它变成瞎眼的杀戮机器！",en:"The wearer of this bracelet should be very proud. It was originally intended as a muzzle for Rascal, and it was the only thing that stopped him from being a busy, dizzy, killing machine!"};
descriptions["21541"]={cn:"锁...锁...锁链之靴！小心，这些链条都在动！也许这双靴子的存在是对所有你击败动物的惩罚的象征...",en:"Ch-ch-ch-ch-chained boots! Look out, you rock and roller! Maybe this is punishment for all the victims you\'ve killed in your days..."};
descriptions["21542"]={cn:"这件披风散发着一股刺鼻的气味。其实只是多种怪物毛皮的混合物而已。",en:"Fair enough, this cloak has a very strong and unpleasant odor. It\'s basically a mix of various monster furs."};
descriptions["21543"]={cn:"每天晚上钻地前都要对着地面闻30秒。这样你有充分的时间穿上睡衣，梳梳头发，然后再尖叫着冲出去喊救命。",en:"This amulet starts snuffling 30 seconds before night-time fire drills, which should give you time to put on your pajama bottoms and comb your hair before going outside."};
descriptions["21544"]={cn:"把你的手指塞进去！",en:"Put your finger in the hole!"};
descriptions["21545"]={cn:"这件肩甲属于你另一个时代的朋友：格雷十三。",en:"This epaulettes belonged to your friend from another age: Gray XIII."};
descriptions["21546"]={cn:"即使属于格雷十三，这条腰带也只有一道防线。不知道为什么...",en:"Even though it belonged to Gray XIII, this belt only has a single defense. Can\'t think why..."};
descriptions["21547"]={cn:"虽然这件斗篷很漂亮，但它最多只能让你指挥一团香蕉。话说回来，这其实也不算太寒酸。",en:"While classy, this cloak won\'t let you command much more than a regiment of Citronanas. Then again, that\'s actually not too shabby."};
descriptions["21548"]={cn:"把戒指戴在不同的手指上会有不同的效果。这些细节都写在一份神秘的古代手稿中，但不幸的是，它似乎无法翻译。",en:"Putting this ring on different fingers gets different results. The details were all written down in a mysterious ancient manuscript, but unfortunately, it seems to be untranslatable."};
descriptions["21549"]={cn:"这个可爱的小皇冠非常适合你，就像地穴兽一样！",en:"This cute little crown fits you like a Drheller!"};
