descriptions["21591"]={cn:"和你的朋友们整夜狂欢吧！",en:"This will keep your friends on their toes all night long!"};
descriptions["21597"]={cn:"沃土吹灭了 5 岁生日蜡烛！所以何不来一场竹奶盛宴呢？",en:"WAKFU\'s blown out its 5th birthday candles! So why don\'t you have a blowout on Bamboo Milk?"};
descriptions["21598"]={cn:"这根魔杖以前被十二世界的僧侣们用来缩减他们的人格，减少他们犯戒的欲望，而它实际上可以缩小任何东西的尺寸！",en:"Formerly used by the Monks of the World of Twelve to shrink their attributes and lessen their desire to sin, this wand can actually reduce anything in terms of size!"};
descriptions["21599"]={cn:"这个神奇的护符让你能够在由奥古之泪形成的磷光之水中游泳，否则你肯定会马上溺水！",en:"This fantastic amulet allows you to swim in the luminescent waters produced by a concentrate of Ogrest\'s Tears. Without it, you\'ll surely drown almost instantly!"};
descriptions["21600"]={cn:"给米歇尔加入怪物搜藏的蚌蚌蛋。",en:"A Mollusky Egg for Mishell\'s monster collection."};
descriptions["21601"]={cn:"如果你把这个华丽的贝壳放在你的耳朵旁，你可以听到奥古的嚎叫。",en:"If you put this splendid shell to your ear, you can hear Ogrest howl."};
descriptions["21602"]={cn:"如此强大的眼泪，如果你把它直接喝下去，它会立即杀死你！",en:"A tear so powerful that it would kill you instantly if you swallowed it pure!"};
descriptions["21603"]={cn:"奥铎曼为你准备了第一剂解药，能够对抗泽尼特的瘴气。",en:"Otomai has prepared your first antidote to drink, which combats the effects of Zinit Miasma."};
descriptions["21604"]={cn:"牧民的生活是有弊处的，但是你得做你必须做的事...",en:"There are downsides to the life of a Trapper, but you\'ve gotta do what you\'ve gotta do..."};
descriptions["21605"]={cn:"非常柔顺...",en:"Very silky..."};
descriptions["21606"]={cn:"一堆半消化的泥土，让放弃冒险者生活的人有一小块平静的地方待着。",en:"A patch of half-digested earth, for those who are considering giving up life as an adventurer in order to settle down on a quiet little plot of land."};
descriptions["21607"]={cn:"这张床硬的像石头一样！",en:"This bed is as hard as stone!"};
descriptions["21608"]={cn:"这是一张为胃口堪比奥古的人准备的宽敞桌子！",en:"A spacious table for those who have an appetite to rival that of Ogrest!"};
descriptions["21609"]={cn:"用真正的泽尼特山岩石做成的橱柜。",en:"A cupboard made out of real Mount Zinit rocks."};
descriptions["21610"]={cn:"用真正的泽尼特山岩石做成的床头柜。",en:"A dresser made from real Mount Zinit rocks."};
descriptions["21611"]={cn:"这屏风完全不透光！",en:"This screen won\'t let any light in!"};
descriptions["21612"]={cn:"一种生长后可能致命的植物！",en:"A plant whose growth could be deadly!"};
descriptions["21613"]={cn:"一个挑战你极限的游戏！",en:"A game that will push your limits!"};
descriptions["21614"]={cn:"一座祭坛，为所有在攀登泽尼特山时迷路的冒险者祈祷。",en:"An altar to pray at for all the adventurers lost on the climb up Mount Zinit."};
descriptions["21615"]={cn:"美丽记忆，永久珍藏。",en:"A nice trophy for your personal collection."};
descriptions["21616"]={cn:"美丽记忆，永久珍藏。",en:"A nice trophy for your personal collection."};
descriptions["21617"]={cn:"你对一个真正爱过你的人唯一的记忆。",en:"Your only memory of a being who really, truly loved you."};
descriptions["21618"]={cn:"美丽记忆，永久珍藏。",en:"A nice trophy for your personal collection."};
descriptions["21619"]={cn:"美丽记忆，永久珍藏。",en:"A nice trophy for your personal collection."};
descriptions["21620"]={cn:"给予那些走在泽尼特山海滩上，选择活得像泽尼特之人的称号。",en:"A title for those who\'ve chosen the Zinitude Attitude by walking on the beaches of Mount Zinit."};
descriptions["21621"]={cn:"现在是爱的季节，你已经决定穿上你最漂亮的衣服。没有人怀疑你的魅力；无论如何，你不怀疑。",en:"It\'s the season of love, and you\'ve decided to wear your most beautiful finery for the occasion. No one doubts your charm; in any case, not you."};
descriptions["21622"]={cn:"不管针脚是否露出；用爱制成的坐垫是您一生的陪伴。",en:"No matter if the stitching comes out; this cushion made with love is your partner for life."};
descriptions["21623"]={cn:"一个柔软的、可爱的玩具，让你可以多多...抱着它，当然了！",en:"A soft, cuddly toy, so you can give it lots of... cuddles, of course!"};
descriptions["21624"]={cn:"小小的享受，可能会让你毁灭。",en:"The little treat which might just be your undoing."};
descriptions["21625"]={cn:"小小的享受，可能会让你毁灭。",en:"The little treat which might just be your undoing."};
descriptions["21626"]={cn:"这份精华包含了怪物的灵魂，能把力量注入几乎所有类型的物品。",en:"This essence contains monsters\' souls, and can instill their power into almost all types of items."};
