descriptions["21732"]={cn:"獾兽的坏脾气经常让他们改变战术。像是在你砍完对手后，用这副多毛肩甲清理武器。",en:"The bad mood of Badgeroxes often makes them change their tactics. Like cleaning your weapon with these Hairpaulettes, once you\'ve finished chopping opponents."};
descriptions["21733"]={cn:"镶嵌了獾兽尖牙的戒指，非常适合打断人的牙齿。",en:"A Badgerox Fang set into a ring, perfect for breaking people\'s teeth."};
descriptions["21734"]={cn:"镶嵌了獾兽尖牙的戒指，非常适合打断人的牙齿。",en:"A Badgerox Fang set into a ring, perfect for breaking people\'s teeth."};
