descriptions["21738"]={cn:"这胸甲有一个不同寻常的特点，能够掩盖即使没有它，你也有同多的毛的事实。",en:"This breastplate has the unusual feature of hiding the fact that you\'re just as hairy even without it."};
descriptions["21739"]={cn:"属于一名死于阿利莫堡围困中的牧民，以其爱国心及制作獾兽标本的兴趣而闻名。",en:"Slimy Rockett, who died during the siege of Fort Alimo, was a trapper who was well known for his commitments to his nation, but also for his hobby of stuffing Badgeroxes."};
descriptions["21740"]={cn:"属于一名死于阿利莫堡围困中的牧民，以其爱国心及制作獾兽标本的兴趣而闻名。",en:"Slimy Rockett, who died during the siege of Fort Alimo, was a trapper who was well known for his commitments to his nation, but also for his hobby of stuffing Badgeroxes."};
