descriptions["21742"]={cn:"一条有着獾兽尖牙和毛的饰品。你可以自己去思考制作这条挂坠的人有多么古怪的信仰。",en:"A charm bringing together a fang and a tuft of Badgerox hair. We\'ll let you wonder what strange belief whoever made this pendant had."};
descriptions["21743"]={cn:"一条有着獾兽尖牙和毛的饰品。你可以自己去思考制作这条挂坠的人有多么古怪的信仰。",en:"A charm bringing together a fang and a tuft of Badgerox hair. We\'ll let you wonder what strange belief whoever made this pendant had."};
descriptions["21744"]={cn:"并非獾兽厨师在制作这件披风时没有发挥创意，而是这只是一件换下来当披风的围裙。",en:"Badgerox chefs weren\'t lacking in ingenuity when they made this cape, seeing as it\'s just an apron that\'s taken a backseat."};
descriptions["21745"]={cn:"并非獾兽厨师在制作这件披风时没有发挥创意，而是这只是一件换下来当披风的围裙。",en:"Badgerox chefs weren\'t lacking in ingenuity when they made this cape, seeing as it\'s just an apron that\'s taken a backseat."};
descriptions["21746"]={cn:"并非獾兽厨师在制作这件披风时没有发挥创意，而是这只是一件换下来当披风的围裙。",en:"Badgerox chefs weren\'t lacking in ingenuity when they made this cape, seeing as it\'s just an apron that\'s taken a backseat."};
descriptions["21747"]={cn:"以其能够准确命中弱点的能力而命名，这把双手剑效果卓越，尤其是在你的敌人对它没有提防的时候。",en:"Named for its ability to hit right where it hurts, this two-handed sword will prove to be highly effective, especially when your enemy doesn\'t suspect it."};
descriptions["21748"]={cn:"以其能够准确命中弱点的能力而命名，这把双手剑效果卓越，尤其是在你的敌人对它没有提防的时候。",en:"Named for its ability to hit right where it hurts, this two-handed sword will prove to be highly effective, especially when your enemy doesn\'t suspect it."};
descriptions["21749"]={cn:"尖端非常细的匕首，使用得当还能做为缝合用...",en:"A dagger with a very fine point, which, when used properly, allows very effective sutures to be performed..."};
descriptions["21750"]={cn:"尖端非常细的匕首，使用得当还能做为缝合用...",en:"A dagger with a very fine point, which, when used properly, allows very effective sutures to be performed..."};
descriptions["21751"]={cn:"也有紫红色的。",en:"Also comes in fuchsia pink."};
descriptions["21752"]={cn:"也有紫红色的。",en:"Also comes in fuchsia pink."};
descriptions["21753"]={cn:"尤其是在疲累的时候，如果你既好斗又暴力，那这顶头盔就很适合你。",en:"If you\'re aggressive and violent, especially when tired, this helmet\'s for you."};
descriptions["21754"]={cn:"尤其是在疲累的时候，如果你既好斗又暴力，那这顶头盔就很适合你。",en:"If you\'re aggressive and violent, especially when tired, this helmet\'s for you."};
descriptions["21755"]={cn:"粗糙的鞣制、简易的皮革，无法抵挡对手的攻击。然而，有些人享受痛苦。",en:"A clumsily tanned, simple leather, which won\'t stop your opponents\' attacks. Then again, some people enjoy the pain."};
descriptions["21756"]={cn:"粗糙的鞣制、简易的皮革，无法抵挡对手的攻击。然而，有些人享受痛苦。",en:"A clumsily tanned, simple leather, which won\'t stop your opponents\' attacks. Then again, some people enjoy the pain."};
descriptions["21757"]={cn:"獾兽毛和仿制披风...天啊！",en:"Badgerox hair and potanicloakery... geez!"};
descriptions["21758"]={cn:"我的披风！我的披风呢！？那不是你的！",en:"MY CAPE! WHAT ABOUT MY CAPE!? IT\'S NOT YOURS!"};
descriptions["21759"]={cn:"最好不要惹他们，否则事情很快就会变得很刺激...",en:"Better not mess with them, otherwise things could quickly get spicy..."};
descriptions["21760"]={cn:"最好不要惹他们，否则事情很快就会变得很刺激...",en:"Better not mess with them, otherwise things could quickly get spicy..."};
descriptions["21761"]={cn:"缝抑或不缝，这正是问题的本质所在。",en:"To knit or not to knit, that is the knitty-gritty of the question."};
descriptions["21762"]={cn:"即使效果不差，这枚珠宝的装饰仍饱受争议。",en:"Although effective, the decoration of this jewel remains debatable."};
descriptions["21763"]={cn:"皮革、牙齿以及毛发：正是这些使得猎户腰带是一条好腰带。",en:"Leather, teeth and hair: what makes the Trapper Belt great."};
descriptions["21764"]={cn:"由柔顺的白色獾兽毛制成，总是能保持洁净。",en:"Made from silky white Badgerox hair, this cape always stays clean."};
descriptions["21765"]={cn:"足以把敌人弄得头下脚上。",en:"Enough to turn your enemies upside-down."};
descriptions["21766"]={cn:"足以把敌人弄得头下脚上。",en:"Enough to turn your enemies upside-down."};
descriptions["21767"]={cn:"熊獾兽家族的腰带，既不会太松也不会太紧。",en:"This belt is the model that is neither too loose nor too tight, used by the Beardger family."};
descriptions["21768"]={cn:"熊獾兽家族的腰带，既不会太松也不会太紧。",en:"This belt is the model that is neither too loose nor too tight, used by the Beardger family."};
descriptions["21769"]={cn:"发酵的牛奶有着强大的治愈功能，即使只是弄在脖子附近。有让你感到惊讶吗？喝醉了才会相信这种事。",en:"Fermented Romel milk has powerful curing properties, even if it\'s only worn around the neck. Does that surprise you? It\'s got to be drunk to be believed."};
descriptions["21770"]={cn:"发酵的牛奶有着强大的治愈功能，即使只是弄在脖子附近。有让你感到惊讶吗？喝醉了才会相信这种事。",en:"Fermented Romel milk has powerful curing properties, even if it\'s only worn around the neck. Does that surprise you? It\'s got to be drunk to be believed."};
descriptions["21771"]={cn:"注意：与同名的凉鞋不同，不建议尝试把这把匕首弄在脚上走路。",en:"Be careful: unlike the sandals of the same name, it\'s inadvisable to try and walk with this dagger on your feet."};
descriptions["21772"]={cn:"以去毛后的獾兽皮制成。",en:"Armor made from Badgerox skin, from which all hair has been removed."};
descriptions["21773"]={cn:"你怎么会想要把这东西放在头上！？?",en:"What\'s the idea of putting this thing on your head!?"};
descriptions["21774"]={cn:"如此尖锐而又坚硬的牙齿能用来切割石头。",en:"A pointy and solid fang like this can be used to cut stone."};
descriptions["21775"]={cn:"獾兽用它们来挖洞和撕开猎物，甚至还能切开最坚硬的胸甲。",en:"Badgeroxes use these to dig their burrows and tear apart their prey. They can even slice open the most solid breastplates."};
descriptions["21776"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few drops should suffice."};
descriptions["21777"]={cn:"这簇毛发既柔顺又有臭味；使用前需要好好清洗一下。",en:"This tuft of hair is as silky as it is smelly; it needs a good clean before you put it to use."};
descriptions["21778"]={cn:"獾兽的尾巴因其浓密而厚实的皮毛而备受赞赏，这些皮毛可以用来制作坚固的零件。",en:"The Badgerox Tail is highly appreciated for its rich and thick fur, which is used to make solid components."};
descriptions["21779"]={cn:"这只眼睛持续瞪着你，仍旧充满了其原主人的怒气。",en:"This eye constantly glares at you, still animated by the rage of its former owner."};
descriptions["21780"]={cn:"美丽记忆，永久珍藏。",en:"A nice trophy for your personal collection."};
descriptions["21781"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。\n打开它只需要两秒！",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with the mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["21782"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。\n打开它只需要两秒！",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with the mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["21783"]={cn:"虽然想说些关于这戒指的趣事，但不幸的是，它真的没什么趣。",en:"It\'d be nice to say something interesting about this ring, but unfortunately, it really is of no interest whatsoever."};
descriptions["21784"]={cn:"这只强大的戒指有个缺点：穿戴者周围永远会围绕着一股清凉的微风。",en:"This powerful ring has one disadvantage: its wearer is permanently surrounded by a slight cool breeze."};
descriptions["21785"]={cn:"务必不要把这个会发出毒气的戒指和氨脂戒搞混了，后者是家务用的。",en:"This ring, which gives off a toxic gas, must not be mistaken for the Ammoniac Ring, which is used to do the housework."};
descriptions["21786"]={cn:"各种色彩的蒸汽散播在泽尼特山上。我们欠约翰·杰克一份光荣。",en:"Many colored vapors are strewn across Mount Zinit. We owe the name of the rose to John Jack."};
descriptions["21787"]={cn:"由天气球精华制作而成的垂饰，会伴随你一生。",en:"A pendant made from Ethernal Essence, which will stay with you your entire life."};
descriptions["21788"]={cn:"由沙漠之风制成，能让穿戴者保持温暖。",en:"Made from a desert wind, this amulet keeps its wearer warm."};
descriptions["21789"]={cn:"穿上这副肩甲让人了解到，战斗实用性与软滑内衬是能够兼具的。",en:"Wearing these epaulettes shows that great worth in combat is not incompatible with a smooth and creamy inside."};
descriptions["21790"]={cn:"你受够熏满油烟的屋梁了吗？别忘了连这个一起清理。",en:"Have you had it up to the rafters with all of the smoke and soot? Then don\'t forget to sweep these ones."};
descriptions["21791"]={cn:"这条腰带有时会放出吵杂、不悦的蒸汽。记得要穿对地方，意即，不是你平常会穿的地方。",en:"This belt sometimes gives off noisy, unpleasant vapors. Wear it in the right place; in other words, not where you\'d usually wear it."};
descriptions["21792"]={cn:"戴着这件腰带，你感觉像个在萨弗基亚采棉花时，弄丢心爱鱼勾的钓虾人，而且还因为忘记穿外套得了感冒。",en:"Wearing this belt, you feel, definitively, like a Grawn fisherman who lost his favorite fishhook trying to gather Cotton in Sufokia, and who has caught a cold because he forgot to put his jacket on."};
descriptions["21793"]={cn:"这件护具冒出的烟令你周遭的人感到困扰；不仅有害而且会使穿戴者成瘾。禁止于公共场所使用。",en:"This ventral protection gives off smoke that bothers those around you; it causes harmful effects and can be addictive for the wearer. It is forbidden from being used in public areas."};
descriptions["21794"]={cn:"这件外套的某些版本能让数人同时使用。如果你们无法全部进去，可以把它传给别人。",en:"Some versions of this jacket can be used by several people at the same time. If you can\'t all get in at once, you can always pass it around."};
descriptions["21795"]={cn:"穿起来温度非常高，这双靴子会烫伤你的脚，让你跳得高又跑得快。",en:"Worn at high temperature, these boots scald your feet, making your jump higher and run faster."};
descriptions["21796"]={cn:"由Otto大厨所发明，用来料理他在脚指缝找到的蘑菇。",en:"Invented by Otto Chef to cook mushrooms he found between his toes."};
descriptions["21797"]={cn:"经由灰烬龙残骸的加热后，除了有敏感部位发汗的风险外，这是最舒服的裤子了。",en:"Heated thanks to Ashdragon\'s remains, these pants are some of the most comfortable, despite the risk of sweating in irritating places."};
descriptions["21798"]={cn:"戴着一顶这么棒的头盔，你能边吼着“在我白旗之处集结！”边带领队伍进入战斗。",en:"Crowned with such a magnificent piece of headgear, you\'ll be able to guide your team into combat while crying \"rally to my white banner!\"."};
descriptions["21799"]={cn:"大部分冒险者用湿毛巾来滤掉附近的蒸气。戴着这兜帽的仁兄偏好滤掉新鲜空气。",en:"Most adventurers use a damp towel to filter nearby vapors. This hood\'s users prefer to filter fresh air."};
descriptions["21800"]={cn:"这顶帽子能让不着边际的人务实点。当作内衣穿也有同样效果，真的。",en:"This hat allows people who have their head in the clouds to step on the gas a little. Can also be used as underwear for the same effect. No, seriously."};
descriptions["21801"]={cn:"这件二合一披风也能当作野餐加热毯使用，让你可以直接在上面烹煮各种食物。",en:"This 2-in-1 cape can also be used as a heated picnic blanket, so much so that you can cook various foods straight on it."};
descriptions["21802"]={cn:"比传统斗蓬无害的斗蓬，有多种口味可供选择：萝卜、甜瓜、玉米等。",en:"A cloak that is less harmful than traditional cloaks, available in several flavors to choose from: Cawwot, Melon, Corn, etc."};
descriptions["21803"]={cn:"一大张布披让你保持温暖。要记得穿在腰间。",en:"A large drape to keep you warm. Lots."};
descriptions["21804"]={cn:"啸风项链在周围风和蒸汽的带动下能产生可观的能量。据说其旋转的力量极强，要是有好奇的布丁靠太近，有可能会被吹散到十二世界的四角。",en:"The Amulet of Howlieng Wind produces impressive energy in the presence of ambient winds and vapors. It is said that the power of its rotation is so strong that a curious Puddly could end up being scattered to the four corners of the World of Twelve if it came too close."};
descriptions["21805"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。\n打开它只需要两秒！",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with the mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["21806"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。\n打开它只需要两秒！",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with the mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["21807"]={cn:"耶咿！",en:"Yay!"};
descriptions["21808"]={cn:"挥舞这把武器让你的对手陷入烟雾之中。",en:"Twirl this weapon to engulf your opponent in a cloud of smoke."};
descriptions["21809"]={cn:"斩开破晓浓雾不可或缺的武器。",en:"The essential weapon to cut your way out of a thick, morning-after fog."};
descriptions["21810"]={cn:"迅如风、疾如电，这把匕首能在一瞬之间了结你的对手。",en:"As fast as the wind, as quick as lightning, this dagger will strike down your opponent on the spot."};
descriptions["21811"]={cn:"据闻这把烟管是和睦的象征，但直接拿去殴打敌人会简单得多。",en:"It is said that this pipe is a symbol of peace, but it could be simpler just to hit your enemies with it."};
descriptions["21812"]={cn:"沉着地去熏你的敌人。",en:"Calmly smoke your enemies."};
descriptions["21813"]={cn:"如果你从远处看到一列移动的烟雾，大概是有人穿着辉耀披风在跑动。",en:"If you spot a moving column of smoke from afar, it\'s probably someone running with their Panache Cloak equipped."};
descriptions["21814"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将天气球的生命气息收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the Ethernals\' breath of life contained in this flask! A few drops should suffice."};
descriptions["21815"]={cn:"据说有些粗心的人在采集时没有做好适当的防护，于是当下就被溶解了。",en:"It\'s said that some careless trappers tried to harvest this breath without the proper protection, and were dissolved on the spot."};
descriptions["21816"]={cn:"这是天气球所吐出的最后一口气，包含了他们的精华。",en:"This sigh is the last one the Ethernals ever produced, which contains their quintessence."};
descriptions["21817"]={cn:"这气体会在口中留下些微苦味，但由于这不是拿来吃的所以无所谓。",en:"This gas leaves a bitter taste in the mouth, but that doesn\'t really matter since it wasn\'t made to be ingested."};
descriptions["21818"]={cn:"这气体闻起来很刺鼻。小心别中毒了。",en:"This gas gives off a smell that makes your nose tingle. Be careful not to get poisoned."};
descriptions["21819"]={cn:"你掐灭灰烬龙的火焰后，唯一剩下的东西。",en:"This is all that remains of Ashdragon, after you snuffed out his flames."};
descriptions["21820"]={cn:"美丽记忆，永久珍藏。",en:"A nice trophy for your personal collection."};
descriptions["21821"]={cn:"收集 100 块碎片，合成高阶精神护符。",en:"Collect 100 of these fragments to create an Ellie\'s Deluxe Mental Amulet."};
descriptions["21822"]={cn:"这种头饰的魅力不在于它让你看起来秃顶，而在于你接受了它。",en:"This headgear\'s charm lies not in the fact that it makes you look bald, but more in the fact that you accept it."};
descriptions["21823"]={cn:"这个胸甲是一个想要坚不可摧的人制作的，除了里面。",en:"This breastplate was created by someone who wanted to be impenetrable, except on the inside."};
descriptions["21824"]={cn:"尽管经过了几个世纪，这些祖传的鞋子并没有失去它们的主要用途：它们仍然是很好的烧烤签子。",en:"Despite the centuries, these ancestral boots haven\'t lost their main use: they\'re still great barbecue skewers."};
descriptions["21825"]={cn:"蛋龙每年都要举行一次造型比赛。最丑的衣服就这样被抛弃了，这就是为什么你最后穿着这件披风的原因...",en:"Dreggons come together once a year for a style contest. The most ugly attire is thus abandoned, Which explains how you ended up wearing this cloak..."};
descriptions["21826"]={cn:"这种头饰的魅力不在于它让你看起来秃顶，而在于你接受了它。",en:"This headgear\'s charm lies not in the fact that it makes you look bald, but more in the fact that you accept it."};
descriptions["21827"]={cn:"这个胸甲是一个想要坚不可摧的人制作的，除了里面。",en:"This breastplate was created by someone who wanted to be impenetrable, except on the inside."};
descriptions["21828"]={cn:"尽管经过了几个世纪，这些祖传的鞋子并没有失去它们的主要用途：它们仍然是很好的烧烤签子。",en:"Despite the centuries, these ancestral boots haven\'t lost their main use: they\'re still great barbecue skewers."};
descriptions["21829"]={cn:"一个蛋壳形状的戒指。",en:"An egg-squisite ring."};
descriptions["21830"]={cn:"蛋龙每年都要举行一次造型比赛。最丑的衣服就这样被抛弃了，这就是为什么你最后穿着这件披风的原因...",en:"Dreggons come together once a year for a style contest. The most ugly attire is thus abandoned, Which explains how you ended up wearing this cloak..."};
descriptions["21831"]={cn:"许多学识渊博的人试图制造一种像蛋龙壳一样坚固的材料，但从这个盾牌来看，并没有多少人成功。",en:"Many knowledgeable people have tried to craft a material that is as solid as Dreggon Shells, but without much success, judging by this shield."};
descriptions["21832"]={cn:"这是一条无力的双头蛋龙能够穿戴的配件。",en:"This is the kind of accessory an ineffective Dregger can wear."};
descriptions["21833"]={cn:"双头蛋龙的目的就是让你戴上这只戒指。知道这件事后，你确定还想戴上它吗？",en:"The Dregger\'s aim is to slip it on your finger. Knowing this, are you still so sure you want to wear it?"};
descriptions["21834"]={cn:"不，不是那种可以放进口袋的腰带，而是有很多口袋的腰带。这样子更有用。",en:"No, not as in a belt that you can fit in your pocket, but a belt with many pockets. That\'s far more useful."};
descriptions["21835"]={cn:"早餐，有人要吗？",en:"Breakfast, anyone?"};
descriptions["21836"]={cn:"不足以让你将双脚塞进去。",en:"The Foot Ring isn\'t big enough for you to put both feet in it."};
descriptions["21837"]={cn:"学习是一生的事。你最好尽快开始，因为“一生”实际上很长的。",en:"Learning is a lifelong experience. You\'re best starting as early as possible, because \"lifelong\" is indeed quite long."};
descriptions["21838"]={cn:"皮匠们总是对如何将物品用于奇怪用途方面特别有天分...",en:"Leather Dealers have always been talented when it comes to finding unorthodox uses for items..."};
descriptions["21839"]={cn:"这双靴子属于一只会吃蛋龙孩子的食人魔。",en:"These boots belonged to an Ogre who ate Dreggon children."};
descriptions["21840"]={cn:"它真的挺坚固。",en:"It really is quite strong."};
descriptions["21841"]={cn:"摩擦左肩会出现邪恶的精灵永恒地折磨你；摩擦右肩会出现善良的精灵实现你最大的愿望。还是左右反过来才是对的？",en:"Rub the left epaulette and an evil genie will torment you for all eternity; rub the right one and a good genie will make your greatest wish come true. Or is it the other way around?"};
descriptions["21842"]={cn:"那些比任何人早一步知道情报的人，有着重大的责任。别跟人说这条腰带的功能！",en:"A great responsibility weighs on those who have information before anyone else. Don\'t tell anyone what this belt does!"};
descriptions["21843"]={cn:"这条来自上古时代的护符在战斗中很有帮助，能够保护你免于失去斗志并直取要害。",en:"This amulet from the Dofus Era will make all the difference in combat by protecting you from a lack of ambition. And hits to the throat."};
descriptions["21844"]={cn:"这种头饰的魅力不在于它让你看起来秃顶，而在于你接受了它。",en:"This headgear\'s charm lies not in the fact that it makes you look bald, but more in the fact that you accept it."};
descriptions["21845"]={cn:"这个胸甲是一个想要坚不可摧的人制作的，除了里面。",en:"This breastplate was created by someone who wanted to be impenetrable, except on the inside."};
descriptions["21846"]={cn:"尽管经过了几个世纪，这些祖传的鞋子并没有失去它们的主要用途：它们仍然是很好的烧烤签子。",en:"Despite the centuries, these ancestral boots haven\'t lost their main use: they\'re still great barbecue skewers."};
descriptions["21847"]={cn:"一个蛋壳形状的戒指。",en:"An egg-squisite ring."};
descriptions["21848"]={cn:"蛋龙每年都要举行一次造型比赛。最丑的衣服就这样被抛弃了，这就是为什么你最后穿着这件披风的原因...",en:"Dreggons come together once a year for a style contest. The most ugly attire is thus abandoned, Which explains how you ended up wearing this cloak..."};
descriptions["21849"]={cn:"许多学识渊博的人试图制造一种像蛋龙壳一样坚固的材料，但从这个盾牌来看，并没有多少人成功。",en:"Many knowledgeable people have tried to craft a material that is as solid as Dreggon Shells, but without much success, judging by this shield."};
descriptions["21850"]={cn:"这是一条无力的双头蛋龙能够穿戴的配件。",en:"This is the kind of accessory an ineffective Dregger can wear."};
descriptions["21851"]={cn:"双头蛋龙的目的就是让你戴上这只戒指。知道这件事后，你确定还想戴上它吗？",en:"The Dregger\'s aim is to slip it on your finger. Knowing this, are you still so sure you want to wear it?"};
descriptions["21852"]={cn:"不，不是那种可以放进口袋的腰带，而是有很多口袋的腰带。这样子更有用。",en:"No, not as in a belt that you can fit in your pocket, but a belt with many pockets. That\'s far more useful."};
descriptions["21853"]={cn:"早餐，有人要吗？",en:"Breakfast, anyone?"};
descriptions["21854"]={cn:"都在食谱里！",en:"It\'s all in the cooking!"};
descriptions["21855"]={cn:"这顶帽子是袖珍型的。它体积更小，几秒钟就可以折叠起来：所有的设计都很便于携带。",en:"This headgear is a pocket model. It\'s smaller and folds up in just a few seconds: all of it has been designed so it\'s easy to transport."};
descriptions["21856"]={cn:"不足以让你将双脚塞进去。",en:"The Foot Ring isn\'t big enough for you to put both feet in it."};
descriptions["21857"]={cn:"无法保证有跟浓稠度一样高的坚硬度。",en:"Its consistency will not reassure you as to its solidity."};
descriptions["21858"]={cn:"穿起来很自在。",en:"You\'ll feel easy wearing these."};
descriptions["21859"]={cn:"胸甲内里的薄膜使得穿戴起来非常舒适。一天结束后，你会感觉像个新生儿一样干净。",en:"The inner membrane of this improvised breastplate makes it very comfortable for its wearer. You\'ll feel as clean as a newborn child at the end of the day."};
descriptions["21860"]={cn:"吽曾是个伟大的蛋龙首领。至少我们是这么认为的。",en:"Goh was a great leader among the Dreggons. That\'s what we think, at least."};
descriptions["21861"]={cn:"学习是一生的事。你最好尽快开始，因为“一生”实际上很长的。",en:"Learning is a lifelong experience. You\'re best starting as early as possible, because \"lifelong\" is indeed quite long."};
