descriptions["21863"]={cn:"这双靴子属于一只会吃蛋龙孩子的食人魔。",en:"These boots belonged to an Ogre who ate Dreggon children."};
descriptions["21864"]={cn:"力量、恐惧、敬畏...那些望向你的人，被你激起了许多东西。",en:"Power, terror, fear... You inspire many things in those who lay their eyes upon you."};
descriptions["21865"]={cn:"有如恒星爆炸般明亮。",en:"As bright as an exploding star."};
descriptions["21866"]={cn:"能用来对抗敌人或喝些有益健康的汤。",en:"You can use it to fight off you enemies or to eat some wholesome soup."};
descriptions["21867"]={cn:"既奢华且强大，这件别致的肩甲因其两颗红宝石而得名。",en:"Luxurious and formidable, these classy epaulettes get their name from the two rubies set into them."};
descriptions["21868"]={cn:"这件黑暗披风属于一位邪恶之主，其为另 8 名邪众之首。所到之处暗夜随行，死亡之声由众口尖啸而出。",en:"A dark coat that belonged to an evil lord, leader of 8 other accomplices. The night walked with them, and death cried forth from their mouths."};
descriptions["21869"]={cn:"每一次死亡都会让它变得更白。",en:"It gets a little whiter with each death."};
descriptions["21870"]={cn:"每一次死亡都会让它变得更白。",en:"It gets a little whiter with each death."};
descriptions["21871"]={cn:"在门上安装金门铰链是谁的主意？更荒谬的是还偷一个当戒指用？",en:"Whose idea was it to install golden door hinges on a door? And whose even more absurd idea was it to steal one an use it as a ring?"};
