descriptions["21956"]={cn:"The Twelvian \"trading HP\" program gives you the chance to step into the shoes (or rather the unwashed clothes) of Otomai, the famous alchemist, for surprising immersion!",en:"The Twelvian \"trading HP\" program gives you the chance to step into the shoes (or rather the unwashed clothes) of Otomai, the famous alchemist, for surprising immersion!"};
descriptions["21957"]={cn:"由比利·通卡和比莉·通卡两兄妹所赞助的服装，与他们享誉盛名的巧克力工厂颜色一样！",en:"Billy and Billie Tonka (brother and sister, respectively) are sponsoring this uniform in the colors of their fabulous, famous chocolate factory!"};
descriptions["21958"]={cn:"今早原力与你同在，让你带着好心情迎接一天的开始去追随你的幸运星！",en:"Because the force is with you this morning, so you can get up on the right side of the bed and follow your lucky star!"};
descriptions["21959"]={cn:"The faithful jersey of the Bonta Gobbowl team! One, two, three... zero!",en:"The faithful jersey of the Bonta Gobbowl team! One, two, three... zero!"};
descriptions["21960"]={cn:"The wonderfulest jersey of the Brakmar Gobbowl team! Krassy, isn\'t it?",en:"The wonderfulest jersey of the Brakmar Gobbowl team! Krassy, isn\'t it?"};
descriptions["21961"]={cn:"The eco-fanatic jersey of the Amakna Gobbowl team! A strong wool for a woven team!",en:"The eco-fanatic jersey of the Amakna Gobbowl team! A strong wool for a woven team!"};
descriptions["21962"]={cn:"The waterproof jersey of the Sufokia Gobbowl team! Unbeatable, even in the mud!",en:"The waterproof jersey of the Sufokia Gobbowl team! Unbeatable, even in the mud!"};
descriptions["21963"]={cn:"The new costume of the Riktus Gobbowl team! Specialists in low blows and low prices!",en:"The new costume of the Riktus Gobbowl team! Specialists in low blows and low prices!"};
descriptions["21964"]={cn:"A Dragosteed skin in Gobbowl colors.",en:"A Dragosteed skin in Gobbowl colors."};
