descriptions["22003"]={cn:"经由灰烬龙残骸的加热后，除了有敏感部位发汗的风险外，这是最舒服的裤子了。",en:"Heated thanks to Ashdragon\'s remains, these pants are some of the most comfortable, despite the risk of sweating in irritating places."};
