descriptions["22005"]={cn:"穿起来温度非常高，这双靴子会烫伤你的脚，让你跳得高又跑得快。",en:"Worn at high temperature, these boots scald your feet, making your jump higher and run faster."};
descriptions["22006"]={cn:"戴着一顶这么棒的头盔，你能边吼着“在我白旗之处集结！”边带领队伍进入战斗。",en:"Crowned with such a magnificent piece of headgear, you\'ll be able to guide your team into combat while crying \"rally to my white banner!\"."};
descriptions["22007"]={cn:"斩开破晓浓雾不可或缺的武器。",en:"The essential weapon to cut your way out of a thick, morning-after fog."};
