descriptions["22009"]={cn:"一大张布披让你保持温暖。要记得穿在腰间。",en:"A large drape to keep you warm. Lots."};
descriptions["22010"]={cn:"迅如风、疾如电，这把匕首能在一瞬之间了结你的对手。",en:"As fast as the wind, as quick as lightning, this dagger will strike down your opponent on the spot."};
descriptions["22011"]={cn:"各种色彩的蒸汽散播在泽尼特山上。我们欠约翰·杰克一份光荣。",en:"Many colored vapors are strewn across Mount Zinit. We owe the name of the rose to John Jack."};
descriptions["22012"]={cn:"你受够熏满油烟的屋梁了吗？别忘了连这个一起清理。",en:"Have you had it up to the rafters with all of the smoke and soot? Then don\'t forget to sweep these ones."};
descriptions["22013"]={cn:"由Otto大厨所发明，用来料理他在脚指缝找到的蘑菇。",en:"Invented by Otto Chef to cook mushrooms he found between his toes."};
