descriptions["22017"]={cn:"大部分冒险者用湿毛巾来滤掉附近的蒸气。戴着这兜帽的仁兄偏好滤掉新鲜空气。",en:"Most adventurers use a damp towel to filter nearby vapors. This hood\'s users prefer to filter fresh air."};
descriptions["22018"]={cn:"沉着地去熏你的敌人。",en:"Calmly smoke your enemies."};
descriptions["22019"]={cn:"这件外套的某些版本能让数人同时使用。如果你们无法全部进去，可以把它传给别人。",en:"Some versions of this jacket can be used by several people at the same time. If you can\'t all get in at once, you can always pass it around."};
descriptions["22020"]={cn:"A pretty costume that will make you look 100 years younger, no matter how old you are, and which will make you love all animals!",en:"A pretty costume that will make you look 100 years younger, no matter how old you are, and which will make you love all animals!"};
descriptions["22021"]={cn:"\"You\'re cold, you like black, so here\'s a Iop costume!\"",en:"\"You\'re cold, you like black, so here\'s a Iop costume!\""};
descriptions["22022"]={cn:"\"You\'re cold, you like red, so here\'s a Iop costume!\"",en:"\"You\'re cold, you like red, so here\'s a Iop costume!\""};
descriptions["22023"]={cn:"Chocolate, chocolat, and yet more chocolate, right at your fingertips!",en:"Chocolate, chocolat, and yet more chocolate, right at your fingertips!"};
descriptions["22024"]={cn:"So that your morning sacrifices will always be \"executed\" to perfection!",en:"So that your morning sacrifices will always be \"executed\" to perfection!"};
