descriptions["22055"]={cn:"Use this wood if you want to really get connected.",en:"Use this wood if you want to really get connected."};
descriptions["22056"]={cn:"棘树的种植是一门艺术...",en:"Planting Brambles is an art..."};
descriptions["22057"]={cn:"制造盾牌时的常用材料。缺点是你的敌人会被挂在上面。",en:"This Bramble Wood is used a lot in shield manufacturing. The only drawback is that your enemies will tend to stick to it."};
descriptions["22058"]={cn:"制造盾牌时的常用材料。缺点是你的敌人会被挂在上面。",en:"This wood is so spicy that you\'ll need to drink lots of Gobbette Milk to reduce the pain. At the same time, it wasn\'t such a good idea to eat such spicy wood..."};
descriptions["22059"]={cn:"But mooom, all my friends have them!",en:"But mooom, all my friends have them!"};
descriptions["22060"]={cn:"用于各种品味奇特的时装。让你看起来像个小土豆，也许你就该这么打扮！",en:"This fiber is used in clothing of questionable taste. It\'ll make you look like a potato sack, but hey, maybe that\'s your thing!"};
descriptions["22061"]={cn:"能给你最爱的人留下深刻印象。",en:"This should be just the thing to impress your sweatheart. Jutey!"};
descriptions["22062"]={cn:"据说这捆黄麻整夜发光，会吸引幽灵骚扰。",en:"People say that this Jute shines all night long and attracts Ghostofs."};
descriptions["22063"]={cn:"让一切菜肴变成味觉盛宴。如果想在热带岛屿上生活，这只是第一道考验。",en:"Here\'s something that will transform the blandest of dishes into a taste sensation! An obligatory gastronomic test you\'ll have to pass if you want to live on a scorching hot island!"};
descriptions["22064"]={cn:"能在你的嘴里掀起惊涛骇浪。\n警告：不吃辣的别碰。",en:"Double-click to transform your whole stack of Ancient Resources into new resources. Ancient Resources need to be used quickly, because they\'ll be removed in a future update."};
descriptions["22065"]={cn:"用手拿过辣椒种子之后，千万别揉眼睛。没有什么东西能帮你解除刺痛！",en:"Don\'t go rubbing your eyes when you\'ve been handling Chili Seeds. Nothing can take the sting out of that!"};
descriptions["22066"]={cn:"干燥后是非常理想的生火材料。或许你在烤蝾螈的时候需要这个。",en:"When dried, Momoss is ideal for starting fires, which is just what you need for roasting a few Salamanders along the way."};
descriptions["22067"]={cn:"这种种子十分适合种在潮湿的月亮岛地下。",en:"This seed takes well when planted in acid Mount Zinit soil."};
descriptions["22068"]={cn:"有弹性又美味，但是你既不能睡在上面也不能吃",en:"Springy and tasty. Can be slept on or eaten."};
descriptions["22069"]={cn:"切碎后卤制或者煲汤，都十分美味。但是要小心了，说不定就是你的最后晚餐。",en:"Chopped, marinated or made into a soup; nettle leaves are absolutely delicious. But watch out, they\'ll probably be the last thing you taste!"};
descriptions["22070"]={cn:"这片染血荨麻叶显然被人用过了。",en:"It certainly looks like this Nettle Leaf was used by someone before you picked it."};
descriptions["22071"]={cn:"我也不知道你为什么要选荨麻...它只会让你双手瘙痒难忍。",en:"I don\'t know why you picked this seed up - it\'ll bring you nothing but itchy legs!"};
descriptions["22072"]={cn:"闪光的不一定是黄金，也有可能是白银。",en:"All that glitters is not Gold. All that glitters is not Gold. Sometimes there\'s a Silver lining, though."};
descriptions["22073"]={cn:"钻石钻石亮晶晶，走近一看却是银。",en:"It shines like crystal or diamond, but it\'s just silver."};
descriptions["22074"]={cn:"相传，曾有一个矿工使用这种石头穿越到异次元去了。信不信由你...",en:"Legend has it that a miner was able to use this ore to access another dimension. But hey, we can\'t just listen to any old yarns..."};
descriptions["22075"]={cn:"土匪头目喜欢用这种装饰老巢。",en:"This obsidian is often used by Riktus bosses who want to give their den a bit of character."};
descriptions["22076"]={cn:"You\'ve asked to keep a replica of this mysterious Haven Bag as a souvenir of your adventures.",en:"You\'ve asked to keep a replica of this mysterious Haven Bag as a souvenir of your adventures."};
descriptions["22077"]={cn:"There were many Salamanders living in the Lava Cave. Now, it\'s no longer possible due to the climate there, which is too cold.",en:"There were many Salamanders living in the Lava Cave. Now, it\'s no longer possible due to the climate there, which is too cold."};
descriptions["22078"]={cn:"对于本地汉尼芭来说，白化蝾螈非常珍贵，以至于有些人甚至认为它们是圣物。",en:"Albino Salamanders are highly prized by local Badgeroxes, so much so that some even believe them to be sacred."};
descriptions["22079"]={cn:"看起来你拥有了可以剔除鱼刺的东西。",en:"There\'s no more meat left on this fish. Maybe the bone is edible?"};
descriptions["22080"]={cn:"To be cooked for a business dinner, so your opponent will be less inclined to drag out negotiations.",en:"To be cooked for a business dinner, so your opponent will be less inclined to drag out negotiations."};
descriptions["22081"]={cn:"The diary of the expert bookkeeper of Mount Zinit\'s mercenaries.",en:"The diary of the expert bookkeeper of Mount Zinit\'s mercenaries."};
descriptions["22084"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。\n打开它只需要两秒！",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with the mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["22085"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。\n打开它只需要两秒！",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with the mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["22086"]={cn:"收集 100 块碎片，合成巫妖披风。",en:"Collect 100 of these fragments to create a Coat of the Sorceror-King."};
descriptions["22087"]={cn:"这把锤子是你在月岛上拿到的月之锤的黑暗版本。它非常坚固，传说中，能轻易击碎坚硬的火山岩。",en:"This hammer is a dark version of the Moon Hammer that you collected on Moon Island. It\'s incredibly sturdy, and according to the legends, allows solid volcanic rock to be easily broken."};
descriptions["22088"]={cn:"一件温暖的兽皮大衣，适合所有身材娇小的人。",en:"A warming fur coat for anyone with small dimensions."};
descriptions["22089"]={cn:"“你高冷，你喜欢黑色，所以这里有一件骑士披风！”",en:"\"You\'re cold, you like black, so here\'s a Iop cape!\""};
descriptions["22090"]={cn:"“你高冷，你喜欢红色，所以这里有一件骑士披风！”",en:"\"You\'re cold, you like red, so here\'s a Iop cape!\""};
descriptions["22091"]={cn:"一件温血斗篷！",en:"A warm-blooded cape!"};
descriptions["22092"]={cn:"一个能唤醒你野兽本能的面具。",en:"A mask that will awaken your animal side."};
descriptions["22093"]={cn:"“你高冷，你喜欢黑色，所以这里有一顶骑士头盔！”",en:"\"You\'re cold, you like black, so here\'s a Iop helmet!\""};
descriptions["22094"]={cn:"“你高冷，你喜欢红色，所以这里有一顶骑士头盔！”",en:"\"You\'re cold, you like red, so here\'s a Iop helmet!\""};
descriptions["22095"]={cn:"这顶王冠迷惑了所有注视着它红宝石的人！",en:"This diadem bewitches anyone who gazes upon its ruby!"};
descriptions["22096"]={cn:"这件小护肩真是既可爱又浓密！",en:"These small epaulettes are really cute and bushy!"};
descriptions["22097"]={cn:"“你高冷，你喜欢黑色，所以这里有一件骑士肩甲！”",en:"\"You\'re cold, you like black, so here are some Iop epaulettes!\""};
descriptions["22098"]={cn:"“你高冷，你喜欢红色，所以这里有一件骑士肩甲！”",en:"\"You\'re cold, you like red, so here are some Iop epaulettes!\""};
descriptions["22099"]={cn:"这件肩甲虽然已有数百年的历史，但仍然完好无损。",en:"These epaulettes are still intact, despite being hundreds of years old."};
descriptions["22100"]={cn:"一条巨大的项链，比起一件漂亮的珠宝，作为遮蔽物更有用。",en:"An enormous necklace, which is more useful for covering your torso than as pretty jewelery!"};
descriptions["22101"]={cn:"“你高冷，你喜欢黑色，所以这里有一双骑士鞋子！”",en:"\"You\'re cold, you like black, so here are some Iop boots!\""};
descriptions["22102"]={cn:"“你高冷，你喜欢红色，所以这里有一双骑士鞋子！”",en:"\"You\'re cold, you like red, so here are some Iop boots!\""};
descriptions["22103"]={cn:"改善血液流动的鞋子！",en:"Boots to help blood flow!"};
