descriptions["22108"]={cn:"There\'s the soul of a leader in this costume, representing the great Kali!",en:"There\'s the soul of a leader in this costume, representing the great Kali!"};
descriptions["22109"]={cn:"从来没有龙能像诺戈那样，做成的填充玩偶后如此柔软而充满感情。",en:"No dragon has ever been so soft and affectionate as Nogord as a stuffed toy."};
descriptions["22110"]={cn:"可怕的尼罗王将君临你的床垫。",en:"The dreadful Nyl King shall become the king of your mattress."};
descriptions["22111"]={cn:"这伪月可爱死了！",en:"You\'d die if you saw a Sham Moon more adorable than this!"};
descriptions["22112"]={cn:"What stuffed toy will you get in this mystery box? Huh?! But it\'s a stuffed toy!",en:"What stuffed toy will you get in this mystery box? Huh?! But it\'s a stuffed toy!"};
descriptions["22113"]={cn:"即使是个填充玩偶，这个僧侣还是有病的。",en:"Even as a stuffed toy, the Monk is still morbid."};
descriptions["22114"]={cn:"查尔斯·亨利，柔软而饱满！",en:"Charles-Henri, all soft and plump!"};
descriptions["22115"]={cn:"使维伦亚脆弱的美丽永垂不朽的一个填充玩偶。",en:"A stuffed toy immortalizing the fragile beauty of Vilenya."};
descriptions["22116"]={cn:"一个用绒毛和纸板做的图塔卡玛！",en:"A Tutaur\'Kama made of wool and cardboard!"};
descriptions["22117"]={cn:"The renowned Bow Meow as a giant stuffed toy for all smitten Bow Meow fans!",en:"The renowned Bow Meow as a giant stuffed toy for all smitten Bow Meow fans!"};
descriptions["22118"]={cn:"谁不梦想着鲁贝克斯就在身边？",en:"Who\'s never dreamed of having Rubilax by their side?"};
descriptions["22119"]={cn:"What stuffed toy will you get in this mystery box?",en:"What stuffed toy will you get in this mystery box?"};
descriptions["22120"]={cn:"这个结合器能够解放菌菇戒指的力量。",en:"This inhibitor will allow you to unlock the Kel\'Dwa\'s powers."};
descriptions["22121"]={cn:"这个结合器能够解放菌菇戒指的力量。",en:"This inhibitor will allow you to unlock the Kel\'Dwa\'s powers."};
descriptions["22122"]={cn:"这个结合器能够解放菌菇戒指的力量。",en:"This inhibitor will allow you to unlock the Kel\'Dwa\'s powers."};
descriptions["22127"]={cn:"有些东西消失了，有些东西则取而代之；香甜南瓜就是活生生的证据。",en:"Something is lost, and something is created in its place; this Pumpkininin is living proof of this."};
descriptions["22128"]={cn:"能在你的嘴里掀起惊涛骇浪。\n警告：不吃辣的别碰。",en:"This chili will create absolute chaos in your mouth.\nWarning: sensitive taste buds should keep away."};
descriptions["22129"]={cn:"这个冷却套件让你能面对火山区的炎热。",en:"This Cooling Kit lets you face the extreme heat of volcanic areas."};
descriptions["22130"]={cn:"A Silo that\'s still extinguished, to be taken to Kali, your favorite Sacrier.",en:"A Silo that\'s still extinguished, to be taken to Kali, your favorite Sacrier."};
descriptions["22131"]={cn:"一旦所有胶囊组合在一起，就能制作出一件隔热装备。",en:"Once all of the capsules are brought together, a heatproof item of equipment can be created."};
descriptions["22132"]={cn:"玄武岩被用做建筑和雕塑。",en:"Basalt is used for construction and making statues."};
descriptions["22133"]={cn:"This Silo will never be lit up again. A circuit failure has turned it into a trendy and completely safe decorative item.",en:"This Silo will never be lit up again. A circuit failure has turned it into a trendy and completely safe decorative item."};
descriptions["22134"]={cn:"A traditional Eliatrope Vessel bunk - basic but very comfortable - for nights spent among the stars.",en:"A traditional Eliatrope Vessel bunk - basic but very comfortable - for nights spent among the stars."};
descriptions["22135"]={cn:"这张桌子足够大，可以举行一日中最重要的会议。",en:"This table is sufficiently large for the most important discussions of the day."};
descriptions["22136"]={cn:"不，这不是冰箱，所以别把你的绵球腿放进去！想想一周后它们的味道有多难闻...",en:"No, this isn\'t a fridge, so don\'t go putting your Gobball Legs in there! Think about how awful they\'d smell after a week..."};
descriptions["22137"]={cn:"一个美丽而精致的梳妆台，由亚兰洛普设计，精益求精、充满禅意。",en:"A beautiful and refined dresser, designed by the Eliatropes, perfect for a tidy, zen space."};
descriptions["22138"]={cn:"虽然这屏风的透明度可能使它不那么实用，但这实在太亚兰洛普了，你无法抗拒！",en:"While its transparency might not make it the most practical of screens, it\'s so Eliatrope that you just can\'t resist it!"};
descriptions["22139"]={cn:"如果你不喜欢每天浇水和清枯叶，那何不来欣赏这些神奇的全息植物呢？",en:"If daily watering and dead leaves aren\'t your thing, why not enjoy one of these marvelous holographic plants instead?"};
descriptions["22140"]={cn:"在飞船这样的密闭空间里放松身体是很重要的，所以我们建议你打开几个传送门来伸展你的胳膊和腿。",en:"It\'s important to relax your body in a confined space like the vessel, so we recommend you open a few portals to stretch your arms and legs."};
descriptions["22141"]={cn:"在这座精致的祭坛上，你的挚爱与你同在。",en:"Your dearly departed are with you throughout your journey on this refined altar."};
descriptions["22142"]={cn:"一股胡椒味扑鼻而来。厨师必备的调味品。",en:"This Gorsegoyle Berry has a very pronounced, peppery flavor. Chefs should always have a few on hand for seasoning their dishes."};
descriptions["22143"]={cn:"只是看它一眼，你就会想要拚命的去触摸它。",en:"All Citronanas should follow the example of this one."};
descriptions["22144"]={cn:"相当坚硬，难以切开。",en:"Hallowed Pooplar Wood is fairly resistant and difficult to split."};
descriptions["22145"]={cn:"如果你有办法带着夏侬蘑菇进去的话，这种稀有的蘑菇受到那些喜欢在厨房里消磨时间的人的珍视。",en:"This rare mushroom is prized by those who love spending time in the kitchen. That is, if you can get in there with Not Mushroom."};
descriptions["22146"]={cn:"此药剂增加你 100 点悟性，使你在战斗结束时获得的经验加倍。此药水持续 2 小时（实际时间），不可叠加。",en:"This potion increases your Wisdom by 100, which doubles the experience gained at the end of fights. This potion lasts 2 hours (real time) and is not stackable."};
descriptions["22147"]={cn:"你不能用煎锅加热它，但是它和罐装面很合得来。",en:"You can\'t heat it in a frying pan, but it goes well with Spaghettos nonetheless."};
descriptions["22148"]={cn:"我的大鳜鱼这样看起来比较大吗？",en:"Does my buttfish look big in this?"};
descriptions["22149"]={cn:"这条深海狼鱼离开了原先生长的池塘，去征服更广阔、更纯净的水域。",en:"This Pond Boowolf grew up in a pond before leaving to conquer wider, purer waters."};
descriptions["22150"]={cn:"美丽记忆，永久珍藏。",en:"A nice trophy for your personal collection."};
descriptions["22151"]={cn:"即使你平时不喜欢吃外国食物，这种面包无论如何都会满足你。看起来一口就足够养活一个成年人好几天了。",en:"Even if you\'re not normally a fan of foreign grub, this bread should please you in any case. It looks like a single mouthful would be enough to sustain a grown man for several days."};
descriptions["22152"]={cn:"这木材将捍卫自己的权利，不会放弃斗争。",en:"This wood will stand up for its rights and won\'t give up the fight."};
descriptions["22153"]={cn:"为了奖励你在地下城的杰出排名，季末宝箱里放了给你的奖赏。打开来看看你得到了什么！",en:"The End-of-Season Chest contains your rewards for being ranked among the best in a dungeon. Open it to find out what you\'ve won!"};
