descriptions["22167"]={cn:"非常有用的武器，sala完了还能吃。",en:"A very useful tool, it has everything you need."};
descriptions["22168"]={cn:"还在犹豫你为谁而战的立场吗？拿起它，没错的。",en:"The perfect shield for when you\'re deciding which side to fight for."};
descriptions["22169"]={cn:"欧洲细作卡卡！这根棒子会帮你打开新世界的大门！",en:"You can start a new life with this hammer."};
