descriptions["22243"]={cn:"他们悄悄告诉你，这个卡牌的使用者维斯特曾经拥有过一段凄美的爱情故事。“哦！坎耶，坎耶 为什么你偏偏是坎耶·维斯特呢？否认你的父亲，抛弃你的姓名吧；也许你不愿意这样做，那么只要你宣誓做我的爱人，我也不愿再姓凯普莱特了。”所以，也没什么大不了的。",en:"They say that these cards once had luscious black locks and were mad about another card player, the Vwest, whispering sweet nothings like... \"Oh Kannye! Kannye! Wherefore art thou, Kannye? Deny thy father and refuse thy name; or if thou wilt not, be but sworn my love, and I\'ll no longer be a Capulet!\" So nothing too serious."};
