descriptions["22346"]={cn:"这就是传说中的莱斯披风！",en:"It\'s a total Cape Rice!"};
descriptions["22347"]={cn:"利用这个腰带和桅杆上的滑轮可以有效的避免涨潮时湿身——老司机们都懂得。",en:"A mast pulley, cleverly tied to make a belt. Will particularly appeal to sailors."};
descriptions["22348"]={cn:"食人族用这些叶子摩擦飞镖，让他的敌人们更加痛苦。",en:"Kanniballs rub their blowpipe darts onto these leaves to cause their enemies more pain."};
descriptions["22349"]={cn:"如果你在椰子上发现一个洞，随时都能从洞口喝一口。",en:"If you find a hole in a Kokonut, you can always use one of these for a quick drink."};
descriptions["22350"]={cn:"看见这棵倒栽树没？虽然摸起来很柔顺，但和伊欧普一样壮。",en:"Can you see this Boabob? It\'s smooth to the touch, but as strong as a Iop!"};
