descriptions["22391"]={cn:"如果你想预测未来，最好带班作你的观众，能让他们慢点意识到你是一个大白痴。",en:"If you want to predict the future, it\'s best if you do it with class so your audience is so swept away with your smoke and mirrors that they don\'t notice what an idiot you are."};
