descriptions["22420"]={cn:"比手表什么的实用多了，这根腰带能看时间，而且精确到秒。",en:"More practical than a watch or a pocket watch, this belt will let you know what time it is and is accurate to the second."};
descriptions["22421"]={cn:"随时准备进入战斗。",en:"Always alert, on fire, ready to let rip."};
descriptions["22422"]={cn:"随时准备接受新的挑战，每个时代都会有新的造型。",en:"Always ready for change, these Innovative Boots renew themselves once an eon. Well, almost."};
