descriptions["22435"]={cn:"适合穿着去参加一场无尽的宴会。",en:"An ideal cloak to wear to banquets that go on and on and on."};
descriptions["22436"]={cn:"这根腰带能绑住许多东西，包括你的裤子。",en:"This belt can keep things up forever, even your trousers."};
descriptions["22437"]={cn:"虽然能穿过时光，但不一定每次都能击中你的敌人。",en:"This arrow, that invariably cuts through the air in the same direction, is not always the most practical tool for reaching your opponents."};
descriptions["22438"]={cn:"这个护肩非常小，这才是它厉害的地方。",en:"The real strength of these epaulettes lies in their delicacy."};
descriptions["22439"]={cn:"实用的匕首，可以用来刺伤另一个次元的人...或者更简单，从背后袭击。",en:"A useful dagger for sticking it to someone from another dimension... Or simply stabbing them in the back."};
descriptions["22442"]={cn:"这件绒毛丰厚的披风能够让你在冬天里既暖和又拉风！",en:"This heavy fur cape will keep you nice and warm in winter!"};
descriptions["22443"]={cn:"这件大号猴毛腰带是提升你男子气概的完美道具。",en:"The big monkey-fur belt is perfect for increasing your virility."};
descriptions["22444"]={cn:"就没人跟你说过你长得像一只小猴子么？！",en:"Hasn\'t anyone told you you look just like a little monkey?!"};
descriptions["22445"]={cn:"你没法教一只老猴子怎么扮鬼脸。那有什么关系呢？没什么关系...",en:"You can\'t teach an old monkey how to pull faces. What\'s that got to do with it? Nothing whatsoever..."};
descriptions["22446"]={cn:"可以放在书架上当漂亮的镇纸。",en:"These would make for a lovely book weight on your shelf."};
descriptions["22447"]={cn:"以月之锤为原型打造，这件武器蕴含着惊人的魔法力量。",en:"Following the example of the Moon Hammer, this weapon contains a surprising, magical power."};
descriptions["22448"]={cn:"一块木雕的小坠饰，上面有着描绘月神的雕刻。",en:"A small pendant of carved wood, sculpted to depict Moon."};
descriptions["22449"]={cn:"这可是你费了九哞二虎之力才搞到的，你就别抱怨款式了！",en:"You\'ve moved heaven and earth to get them, so don\'t complain now!"};
descriptions["22450"]={cn:"这件胸甲能让你穿的像个金刚一样，对吧。",en:"A breastplate that\'s perfect for dressing up as King Kong, right?"};
descriptions["22451"]={cn:"你以前见过喜欢在手上戴戒指的猴子么？",en:"Have you found a monkey who\'d like a ring on their finger?"};
descriptions["22452"]={cn:"这顶头盔曾属于一名专业的飞行员，他在飞过月亮岛上空时失踪。",en:"This helmet belonged to an Imp pilot who disappeared while flying over Moon Island."};
descriptions["22453"]={cn:"一个拥有惊人能力的盾牌，并不仅仅指它的防卫能力，而是指它能够扩大持有者视野的能力。也许秘密藏在这双翡翠眼睛里...",en:"A shield of surprising efficiency, not due to its resistance, but its ability to improve its bearer\'s vision. Maybe it has something to do with the emerald eyes..."};
descriptions["22454"]={cn:"一条蓝绳子上简单的挂着一个奇怪的小娃娃，然而这护符特别实用。",en:"A strange little doll, hanging from a blue cord. It\'s very effective, nonetheless."};
descriptions["22457"]={cn:"我们不可能学到大师或朋友真正的耐心和宽容。只有当我们接触到那些真正令人不快的经历时，才有可能获得这些特质。",en:"We cannot learn real patience and tolerance from gurus or friends. These qualities can be gained only when we come into contact with those who create genuinely unpleasant experiences."};
descriptions["22458"]={cn:"这可以让你的靴子保持初始外观。",en:"This item is used to hide your boots\' visibility."};
descriptions["22459"]={cn:"这可以让你的披风保持初始外观。",en:"This item is used to hide your cape\'s visibility."};
descriptions["22460"]={cn:"这可以让你的头盔保持初始外观。",en:"This item is used to hide your helmet\'s visibility."};
descriptions["22461"]={cn:"这可以让你的肩甲保持初始外观。",en:"This item is used to hide your epaulettes\' visibility."};
descriptions["22462"]={cn:"这可以让你的胸甲保持初始外观。",en:"This item is used to hide your breastplate\'s visibility."};
descriptions["22463"]={cn:"所有冒险者梦寐以求的谜之护符，你值得拥有！",en:"This amulet is highly sought-after by all the high-level adventurers, and you\'ve got it. They\'ll be so jealous!"};
descriptions["22464"]={cn:"最珍贵的指环就应该戴在最好看的那根手指上，让周围的朋友羡慕无比！",en:"Be sure to wear this ring on whatever finger(s) you may use to perform your favorite hand gestures - those on the receiving end will surely appreciate it!"};
descriptions["22465"]={cn:"穿上之后能让您立足悬崖。",en:"Thanks to these boots, you\'ll even be able to go straight up a vertical cliff!"};
descriptions["22466"]={cn:"传说中最别致的斗篷之一，如果说被羽毛蹭得奇痒无比也叫别致的话。",en:"They say this cape is one of the most chic capes. They\'re obviously not taking into account the itchiness caused by the feathers..."};
descriptions["22467"]={cn:"再也不怕被小人戳腰啦。",en:"This will help to protect you from particularly vicious blows."};
descriptions["22468"]={cn:"肩膀上面有什么？不是脑袋就是肩甲！",en:"If you haven\'t got a good head on your shoulders, it\'s best to have good armor on them."};
descriptions["22469"]={cn:"抵挡猛烈攻击，给您加倍信心。",en:"This Breastplate can take even the roughest blows - that oughtta make you a bit more confident in the arena."};
descriptions["22470"]={cn:"重铸这柄剑的人将成为人皇。",en:"Recovering the Steel Beak Sword is an accomplishment few adventurers have managed!"};
descriptions["22471"]={cn:"被一伙土匪从软橡树处劫掠的戒指，不久却被另一伙人给抢走。",en:"After taking this ring from the Soft Oak, it seems that this group of Riktus came across someone stronger than them!"};
descriptions["22472"]={cn:"趁龙猪大人睡觉的时候偷来的宝贝。没了它，龙猪现在只能一肚子横肉露在外边。",en:"This belt was stolen from the Dragon Pig while he slept. Now his gut hangs pendulously, and he\'s furious!"};
descriptions["22473"]={cn:"无主之地，狂怒之地！",en:"All the rage in the Wild Estate!"};
descriptions["22474"]={cn:"据称只有土匪长老才有资格穿戴的斗篷，其实谁穿都一样。",en:"Only the most seasoned Riktus have the right to wear this cape. But that doesn\'t stop everyone from doing it."};
descriptions["22475"]={cn:"从吸血城堡中散落的宝贝，能够号令世上的雌性食尸鬼。",en:"Stolen from Vampyro\'s Castle, this ring will make all the Ghouls tremble! Pretty ghoul, eh?"};
descriptions["22480"]={cn:"The line between Incarnation and Excarnation is as fine and delicate as the surface of this orb.",en:"The line between Incarnation and Excarnation is as fine and delicate as the surface of this orb."};
descriptions["22481"]={cn:"一个有着无与伦比野兽力量的舍利。",en:"An orb of unequaled animal strength."};
descriptions["22482"]={cn:"黑暗烈焰被封在这颗舍利里。",en:"The fire of the darkness is sealed within this orb."};
descriptions["22483"]={cn:"半神的力量存在于这颗舍利中。",en:"The power of a demigod resides within this orb."};
descriptions["22486"]={cn:"一场风暴正在这颗舍利内部肆虐。",en:"A storm is raging inside this orb."};
descriptions["22487"]={cn:"This orb is overflowing with an unrivaled occult power.",en:"This orb is overflowing with an unrivaled occult power."};
descriptions["22488"]={cn:"An orb containing a power that transcends all notion of time.",en:"An orb containing a power that transcends all notion of time."};
descriptions["22489"]={cn:"世间稀有的梦幻装备，得到它你做梦也会笑。",en:"This fantastic helmet is likely one of the rarest that you\'ll ever obtain. You must be dreaming."};
descriptions["22490"]={cn:"This potion increases your Prospecting by 100, which doubles your chance of gaining items at the end of fights. This potion lasts 2 hours (real time) and is not stackable.",en:"This potion increases your Prospecting by 100, which doubles your chance of gaining items at the end of fights. This potion lasts 2 hours (real time) and is not stackable."};
descriptions["22491"]={cn:"这瓶药水会在战斗开始及结束时恢复你所有生命值。效果持续 12 小时（实际时间）并不可堆叠。在战场上没有效果。",en:"This potion returns all of your Health Points to you at the start and end of fights. This potion lasts 12 hours (real time) and is not stackable. It does not work on Battlefields."};
