descriptions["22511"]={cn:"这棵树枝的梦想是成为室内盆景。",en:"This cutting could be whatever it wants to be, but its dream is to be the inspiration for an air freshening spray."};
descriptions["22512"]={cn:"This blackberry seed takes a little while to ripen, so plant it right away!",en:"This blackberry seed takes a little while to ripen, so plant it right away!"};
