descriptions["22517"]={cn:"没有必要为塔德波尔树浇水。它会自动生根发芽，慢慢成长为参天大树。",en:"No need to drown this cutting; it\'ll wriggle its way towards water all by itself before growing into a magnificent tree."};
descriptions["22518"]={cn:"击败叛逆植物的必备武器。",en:"An essential weapon for fighting off rebellious plants."};
descriptions["22519"]={cn:"总是有花汁时不时的从这件武器上滴落，搞的满手黏黏答答的。",en:"Sap constantly trickles out of this weapon, which makes it sticky from end to end."};
descriptions["22520"]={cn:"奇怪的部件。你知道能用来做什么吗？",en:"A strange part. Perhaps you could find a use for it?"};
descriptions["22521"]={cn:"时间沙漏之砂仍然是一个迷。但是沙子的流动是再正常不过的，根本不值一提。",en:"The mystery of the Sandglass of Time remains unsolved. But the sand running through it has nothing to do with it and is so normal its not worth mentioning."};
descriptions["22523"]={cn:"一块充满超能量的护符。",en:"An amulet with overpowered powers..."};
descriptions["22524"]={cn:"一枚佩戴后拥有惊人抗性的戒指。",en:"A ring which makes its wearer surprisingly resistant."};
descriptions["22525"]={cn:"这把品质超群的弓的塑造过程不走寻常路。据说它是往昔的龙的魔法创造出来的。",en:"This bow of extraordinary quality has been shaped in a completely unfamiliar way. It\'s said that it was created by the magic of a dragon from the past."};
descriptions["22526"]={cn:"一件沉重的胸甲，意在模仿棱晶龙强壮的身躯。穿上效果一定惊人。",en:"A heavy breastplate imitating the muscular torso of a Prismatic Dragon. A surprising effect is guaranteed."};
descriptions["22527"]={cn:"这对肩甲布满尖刺，很上档次又能威吓敌人。",en:"Bristling with sharp spikes, these epaulettes give both classy and formidable style."};
descriptions["22528"]={cn:"由一位神秘铁匠用龙鳞铸成，此头盔令敌人闻风丧胆。",en:"Forged from dragon scales by a mythical blacksmith, this helm is formidably effective."};
descriptions["22529"]={cn:"高品质护腿，深受弓手们的喜爱。",en:"Shin pads of high quality, highly prized by archers."};
descriptions["22530"]={cn:"这件外套用龙鳞经特殊手法交错编织而成，可谓巧夺天工。",en:"A coat of amazing finesse, with a very special intertwining of Dragon scales."};
descriptions["22531"]={cn:"小小一枚戒指中蕴藏着狂暴兽性之力。",en:"A small ring harboring a violent, beastly power."};
descriptions["22532"]={cn:"这条非同小可的皮带是由龙鳞做成的，佩戴者会瞬间拥有令人闻风丧胆的卑鄙技能。",en:"This belt, crafted from dragon scales, will give its bearer formidably sneaky skills."};
descriptions["22533"]={cn:"这条项链的取材来自于究极强龙的爪子与鳞片，因而它充满了魔力。",en:"This amulet is crafted from the claws and scales of an ultra-powerful dragon, thereby giving undeniable magical properties."};
descriptions["22534"]={cn:"龙鳞的强化让这件坚固的皮甲变得柔软，而龙鳞间奔流的上古魔力使胸甲的效果更为强大。",en:"Robust leather reinforced with dragon scales makes it supple and strengthens its effects using the ancient magic in the scales."};
