descriptions["22577"]={cn:"收集 100 块碎片，合成扇形盾。",en:"Collect 100 of these fragments to create a Fan Shield."};
descriptions["22578"]={cn:"这个面包和面包板一样平坦。",en:"This bread is as flat as a breadboard."};
descriptions["22579"]={cn:"那黑色且浓郁的口感，就像杯爽口的咖啡。",en:"It\'s black and strong, like a good Makoffee."};
descriptions["22580"]={cn:"可以在戏剧性事件发生时，或非寻常展开发生时愉悦地吃。",en:"To be eaten delectably during dramatic events or out-of-the-ordinary revelations."};
descriptions["22581"]={cn:"神圣的地方在于...味道。",en:"There is something divine in it... its taste."};
descriptions["22582"]={cn:"马上帮你恢复体力，快到想不到。",en:"This bread can regenerate you faster than you can say loaf."};
