descriptions["22584"]={cn:"充满了烘焙者的邪恶灵魂。",en:"Filled with the evil soul of its baker."};
descriptions["22585"]={cn:"这面包同样也需要攀爬。而且需要勇气与毅力。但最终你还是会被碾过。",en:"This bread must also be climbed. It will require bravery and perseverance. But you\'ll end up taking the crunch."};
descriptions["22586"]={cn:"大家都知道里面只是空气而已。",en:"It\'s clear to everyone that it\'s just full of air."};
descriptions["22587"]={cn:"内馅柔软滑顺，夏日经典食物。",en:"So creamy and unctuous in its pie crust, this is a summer\'s day classic."};
descriptions["22588"]={cn:"随时带一些在身上，遇到有看头的战斗时用得上。",en:"Always keep some on you, just in case you stumble upon an interesting fight."};
descriptions["22589"]={cn:"在果冻的尖叫声中，蜜胶树重新焕发了活力。",en:"This gummy lump moves and sways in time with the Jellies\' cries."};
descriptions["22590"]={cn:"据说这把匕首和斯拉姆神的那把同款，不过应该只是某些铁匠的行销手段罢了。",en:"This dagger was allegedly forged from two longblades belonging to the god Sram, but that\'s just some legend invented by the blacksmith so his weapon would sell better."};
