descriptions["22875"]={cn:"小巧可爱，但是锋利无边！",en:"This cute little axe has not lost its edge, and it can fix a sore throat very quickly."};
descriptions["22877"]={cn:"蓬松的大盾，完美吸收攻击。",en:"Cushions blows in case of falls and bounces."};
descriptions["22878"]={cn:"蓬松的大盾，完美吸收攻击。",en:"Cushions blows in case of falls and bounces."};
descriptions["22879"]={cn:"蓬松柔软的腰带。寄上扣子，你觉得舒适极了。",en:"This belt has been pampered its entire life. As soon as the buckle was in place, it knew it was the prettiest."};
descriptions["22880"]={cn:"强大伟岸的福狸光曾把这枚戒指赠予了他心怡的女神，直到他遇到了另一个女神。",en:"The strong and mighty Lenaldix once offered this superb ring to one of his conquests, before asking for it back to give to the next."};
descriptions["22881"]={cn:"据说这把剑是由一种蔬菜制成的，食用这种蔬菜能让人的肌肉变得很发达。",en:"It is said that this sword was made of a vegetable that is renowned for giving big muscles to people who eat it."};
descriptions["22882"]={cn:"适合固定任何衣服，这样你才不会衣衫不整。",en:"This belt allows you to keep any garment in place so that it doesn\'t constantly shift."};
