descriptions["22897"]={cn:"这个披风能让你的功夫变得更厉害。",en:"This cape will surely augment your martial arts skills."};
descriptions["22898"]={cn:"遇到伏兵的时候，临时充当头盔还是不错的。当然，最大的用处还是烧饭，如果有火的话。",en:"Practical as a makeshift helmet in case of ambush, but mostly useful for cooking a good meal or two wherever you go, assuming there\'s fire."};
descriptions["22899"]={cn:"遇到伏兵的时候，临时充当头盔还是不错的。当然，最大的用处还是烧饭，如果有火的话。",en:"Practical as a makeshift helmet in case of ambush, but mostly useful for cooking a good meal or two wherever you go, assuming there\'s fire."};
descriptions["22900"]={cn:"这件道服已经穿了十几年，看上去非常破旧。但它仍然跟以前一样拥有优良的品质。",en:"This kimono was worn for more than a decade; it\'s pretty beat up, but still has all the other characteristics it did so long ago."};
descriptions["22901"]={cn:"这件道服已经穿了十几年，看上去非常破旧。但它仍然跟以前一样拥有优良的品质。",en:"This kimono was worn for more than a decade; it\'s pretty beat up, but still has all the other characteristics it did so long ago."};
descriptions["22902"]={cn:"好好学学福狸的鬼伎俩吧，看看他们是怎么把毒藏在戒指里的。（佐以砂糖，口味尤佳）",en:"You\'ve gotta know how to be sneaky like a Lenald and hide the poison in this ring. (It\'s even better if you\'ve added sugar.)"};
descriptions["22903"]={cn:"好好学学福狸的鬼伎俩吧，看看他们是怎么把毒藏在戒指里的。（佐以砂糖，口味尤佳）",en:"You\'ve gotta know how to be sneaky like a Lenald and hide the poison in this ring. (It\'s even better if you\'ve added sugar.)"};
descriptions["22904"]={cn:"只要你用这件披风把自己包得严严实实，乌鸦就不会来偷你的乳酪了。",en:"When you\'re well camouflaged underneath this cloak, the Crobaks won\'t come to steal your cheese."};
descriptions["22905"]={cn:"只要你用这件披风把自己包得严严实实，乌鸦就不会来偷你的乳酪了。",en:"When you\'re well camouflaged underneath this cloak, the Crobaks won\'t come to steal your cheese."};
descriptions["22906"]={cn:"老福狸都知道好好保护颈椎，老了之后才不会生病。",en:"An old Lenald needs to know when to cover his neck so he doesn\'t become sick as a dog."};
descriptions["22907"]={cn:"正如福狸王闪耀的智慧一般，这胸甲能闪瞎你。",en:"As brilliant as the Empelol himself, the breastplate hurts your eyes a little."};
descriptions["22908"]={cn:"福狸小朋友们从小就会做胜利手势，这个护符相当于胜利手势专业资格鉴定证书。",en:"In childhood, Lenald children learn to make the sign of Victoly, and this amulet is a testament to their gesturing expertise."};
descriptions["22909"]={cn:"福狸小朋友们从小就会做胜利手势，这个护符相当于胜利手势专业资格鉴定证书。",en:"In childhood, Lenald children learn to make the sign of Victoly, and this amulet is a testament to their gesturing expertise."};
descriptions["22910"]={cn:"顶部带有厚厚的毛，削铁如泥大概是不可能的。",en:"With the thick fur on their tops, no one will expect the unquestionable cutting power of these cards."};
descriptions["22911"]={cn:"只要试穿过就会知道有多么舒适，完全不想脱下来。",en:"Once you\'ve tried on this cloak and felt how comfortable it is, you\'ll want to wear it forever. Taking it off would just be illogical."};
descriptions["22912"]={cn:"只要试穿过就会知道有多么舒适，完全不想脱下来。",en:"Once you\'ve tried on this cloak and felt how comfortable it is, you\'ll want to wear it forever. Taking it off would just be illogical."};
descriptions["22913"]={cn:"福狸间流传着这样的谚语：自慧子素于冷静的伦。",en:"A wise old Lenald once said: \"Wisdom only comes to those who lemain tlanquil.\""};
descriptions["22914"]={cn:"福狸间流传着这样的谚语：自慧子素于冷静的伦。",en:"A wise old Lenald once said: \"Wisdom only comes to those who lemain tlanquil.\""};
descriptions["22915"]={cn:"阳光照射强烈的时候，帽子里会飘出一股臭气。但是无论如何这顶帽子都很酷。",en:"It\'s true that, when the sun is very strong, a slight odor of dried meat wafts from the hat, but that doesn\'t change how fabulous you look wearing it."};
descriptions["22916"]={cn:"被福狸重新改造过！一头很锋利，另一头更锋利。简直是致命武器。",en:"It\'s been entirely redesigned by the Lenalds! Not to put too fine a point on it, but it\'s got quite a fine point on it. It\'s deadly, is what we\'re saying here."};
descriptions["22917"]={cn:"所有的黑疯兔地洞为你开启，其实也没几个。",en:"This cloak will open the doors of all the Black Wabbit burrows to you, not that there are many of them."};
descriptions["22918"]={cn:"给真正的黑疯兔！",en:"For real Black Wabbits!"};
descriptions["22919"]={cn:"权力的象征，只有佩戴者才能安全地进入黑疯兔的地盘。",en:"This amulet serves as a sign of authorization, allowing safe passage through certain areas of Black Wabbit occupied territory."};
