descriptions["22945"]={cn:"多少年过去了，黑疯兔家族依然念念不忘祖先当年愚蠢的自我牺牲行为。",en:"It has been passed down through generations of Black Wabbit families to honor and remember the stupid sacrifice of their ancestors."};
descriptions["22946"]={cn:"多少年过去了，黑疯兔家族依然念念不忘祖先当年愚蠢的自我牺牲行为。",en:"It has been passed down through generations of Black Wabbit families to honor and remember the stupid sacrifice of their ancestors."};
descriptions["22947"]={cn:"这件胸甲是用兔毛做的，除了保暖和护身外，还能帮你存储吃饭时掉落的胡萝卜屑。",en:"This breastplate is made from beard hair. It will protect your torso from explosion damage, and it\'ll also store Cawwot crumbs for later."};
descriptions["22948"]={cn:"这件胸甲是用兔毛做的，除了保暖和护身外，还能帮你存储吃饭时掉落的胡萝卜屑。",en:"This breastplate is made from beard hair. It will protect your torso from explosion damage, and it\'ll also store Cawwot crumbs for later."};
descriptions["22949"]={cn:"这鞋子怎么说呢，至少爆炸发生的时候能让你逃快点。",en:"These shoes, extensively tested by Awnie the Emiw, will let you run faster than a bomb explosion!"};
descriptions["22950"]={cn:"护符在此，坏人统统不要过来！",en:"Protects you from those with bad intentions, especially those who want to directly harm you."};
descriptions["22951"]={cn:"看起来不太像匕首，不过从你后面插进去的时候真的很带感哦。",en:"It may not look like much, but it really hurts when it\'s planted in your behind."};
descriptions["22952"]={cn:"看起来不太像匕首，不过从你后面插进去的时候真的很带感哦。",en:"It may not look like much, but it really hurts when it\'s planted in your behind."};
descriptions["22953"]={cn:"这把权杖充满愤怒渴望复仇。它曾为一个杀死毕尔的愤怒新娘所有。",en:"This scepter is marked by rage and thirst for revenge. It used to belong to Beatwix Kiddo."};
descriptions["22954"]={cn:"戴上之后，你会变得比输给龟龟的疯兔还笨。",en:"This ring will make you as nuts as a Black Wabbit at full steam."};
descriptions["22955"]={cn:"戴上之后，你会变得比输给龟龟的疯兔还笨。",en:"This ring will make you as nuts as a Black Wabbit at full steam."};
descriptions["22956"]={cn:"戴上这枚戒指，你感觉怒不可遏。",en:"Like watching Hunee Bow Meow, putting this ring on your finger provokes insatiable rage."};
descriptions["22957"]={cn:"It\'s quite onyxidizable! Your armor will never rust.",en:"It\'s quite onyxidizable! Your armor will never rust."};
descriptions["22958"]={cn:"Wabbits say that armor forged with Mythwil is very heavy and provides little protection. This is actually just a lie so they can keep the mines for themselves...",en:"Wabbits say that armor forged with Mythwil is very heavy and provides little protection. This is actually just a lie so they can keep the mines for themselves..."};
descriptions["22959"]={cn:"Look at this curb, this color, this smell... There\'s no doubt about it: it\'s a stick.",en:"Look at this curb, this color, this smell... There\'s no doubt about it: it\'s a stick."};
descriptions["22960"]={cn:"Isn\'t it magnificent?",en:"Isn\'t it magnificent?"};
descriptions["22961"]={cn:"Be careful: this All Mushray makes a mess everywhere it goes.",en:"Be careful: this All Mushray makes a mess everywhere it goes."};
descriptions["22962"]={cn:"It looks weirdly like a Black Cawwot, doesn\'t it?",en:"It looks weirdly like a Black Cawwot, doesn\'t it?"};
descriptions["22963"]={cn:"This is quite an extraordinary Hydawhey. Even its existence was hidden... until now. Did you come across it due to some sort of miracle?",en:"This is quite an extraordinary Hydawhey. Even its existence was hidden... until now. Did you come across it due to some sort of miracle?"};
descriptions["22964"]={cn:"You can never get enough of it!",en:"You can never get enough of it!"};
descriptions["22965"]={cn:"有史以来，凡是穿着橙色皇袍的疯兔战士对阵福狸时至今未尝败绩！",en:"FACT: no warrior who wears the Oranged Wa into battle will ever fall before a Lenald!"};
descriptions["22966"]={cn:"聪明的人善于问正确的问题。比如，这件披风是正宗的吗？",en:"A prudent question is one half of wisdom. For example, is this cape genuine?"};
descriptions["22967"]={cn:"聪明的人善于问正确的问题。比如，这件披风是正宗的吗？",en:"A prudent question is one half of wisdom. For example, is this cape genuine?"};
descriptions["22968"]={cn:"人不能两次戴上同一个指环...我是说，你可以带两个相同的指环，只是没必要...",en:"It\'s wise not to run in circles."};
descriptions["22969"]={cn:"人不能两次戴上同一个指环...我是说，你可以带两个相同的指环，只是没必要...",en:"It\'s wise not to run in circles."};
descriptions["22970"]={cn:"安心，一切都好。即使不好，也没什么。",en:"It is wisest to keep one\'s organs within oneself."};
descriptions["22971"]={cn:"安心，一切都好。即使不好，也没什么。",en:"It is wisest to keep one\'s organs within oneself."};
descriptions["22972"]={cn:"永远保持清醒，无论是真的还是装的。",en:"It is not wise to lose your head, either figuratively or literally."};
descriptions["22973"]={cn:"头可断，血可流，造型不能丢。",en:"Always keep an open mind, a compassionate heart, and some seriously stylin\' boots."};
descriptions["22974"]={cn:"记忆是智慧之母。",en:"Memory is the mother of all wisdom. Remember to buckle your belt."};
descriptions["22975"]={cn:"记忆是智慧之母。",en:"Memory is the mother of all wisdom. Remember to buckle your belt."};
descriptions["22976"]={cn:"聪明人都会保持颈部温暖。",en:"It is wise to keep your neck warm."};
descriptions["22977"]={cn:"从伤痛中学到经验还是干脆防止受伤，这取决于你。",en:"Turn your wounds into wisdom. Or carry a shield and avoid wounds. Your choice."};
descriptions["22978"]={cn:"不会叫的鸡才会下蛋。",en:"The wise don\'t think aloud. Seriously. Stop it."};
descriptions["22982"]={cn:"远古低语者咒语加持，确保穿戴者万无一失。",en:"Its wearer will be protected by the ancient Whisperers\' murmurs."};
descriptions["22984"]={cn:"适合犹豫不决的统治者，这顶皇冠会教你做出正确选择。",en:"Perfect for indecisive monarchs, this crown will whisper you in the right direction."};
descriptions["22989"]={cn:"嘘，小声点！只是轻轻撞了下而已...",en:"It\'s just (hush!) a little crush (hush!)..."};
descriptions["22990"]={cn:"这把沉重的权杖承载着古代王者的叹息和低语。",en:"This scepter is said to contain the sighs and murmurs of ancient kings."};
descriptions["22992"]={cn:"被咒语束缚着的指环，包含所有抗性。",en:"One ring to bring them all and with a murmur bind them."};
descriptions["22993"]={cn:"真相偏爱热爱冒险的人。",en:"The truth is not for all men, but only for those who seek it."};
descriptions["22994"]={cn:"真相偏爱热爱冒险的人。",en:"The truth is not for all men, but only for those who seek it."};
descriptions["22995"]={cn:"智慧是你知道接下来做什么；而坚持做下去才是真品质。",en:"Wisdom is knowing what to do next; virtue is doing it."};
descriptions["22997"]={cn:"腰带表面覆盖这一层薄薄的冰霜。任何有自尊的冒险者都应该在寒冰奇境试穿这条腰带一星期！",en:"The frost that covers this belt lends it a certain refinement. Any self-respecting adventurer owes it to himself to wear it at least once a week when on Frigost Island!"};
descriptions["22998"]={cn:"腰带表面覆盖这一层薄薄的冰霜。任何有自尊的冒险者都应该在寒冰奇境试穿这条腰带一星期！",en:"The frost that covers this belt lends it a certain refinement. Any self-respecting adventurer owes it to himself to wear it at least once a week when on Frigost Island!"};
descriptions["22999"]={cn:"腰带表面覆盖这一层薄薄的冰霜。任何有自尊的冒险者都应该在寒冰奇境试穿这条腰带一星期！",en:"The frost that covers this belt lends it a certain refinement. Any self-respecting adventurer owes it to himself to wear it at least once a week when on Frigost Island!"};
