descriptions["23107"]={cn:"既能当工具又能当武器，塞拉既用它来贯彻自己的权威也用来伐木。",en:"Half-tool, half-weapon, this ax allows Sylargh to instill authority when he\'s not sawing planks for odd jobs."};
