descriptions["23134"]={cn:"穿上以后会流汗不止。然后你就可以拿汗水来解渴了。",en:"This breastplate will cover your torso and make you sweat unimaginably. Then you can collect the sweat and slake your thirst."};
descriptions["23135"]={cn:"优异的大容量空间能够存放 50 种各类型的资源。\n无法存放装备，且一名角色最多装备两个。",en:"This box can hold up to 50 resources of all types with its exceptional storage space.\nBoxes cannot hold equipment. A character can carry up to 2 boxes."};
descriptions["23136"]={cn:"别勒得太紧，否则就取不下来了...",en:"This belt keeps your body balanced for a perfect stab, every time."};
descriptions["23137"]={cn:"刺瞎你的眼睛，你再也欣赏不到沙漠美景了。",en:"Just be careful not to pop yourself in the eye with one, otherwise you\'ll miss out on all the beautiful desert vistas."};
