descriptions["23140"]={cn:"为了避免缺胳膊断腿，你的敌人会一溜烟从你视线里消失，哇啊啊啊！",en:"In order to keep all their limbs, your enemies will rush to get out of your sight, chop chop!"};
descriptions["23141"]={cn:"在毒热的沙漠，这就是掌仙人保持皮肤清凉的秘诀。",en:"This breastplate you got from the Castucs will keep your skin cool and help you survive the desert."};
