descriptions["23147"]={cn:"进步是从了解自己有多无知开始的。",en:"The only true wisdom is in knowing you know nothing."};
descriptions["23148"]={cn:"拿着它，除了极少数喜欢被刺扎的家伙，不会有谁来亲近你了。",en:"When you\'re carrying this shield, people will want to keep their distance. Rare indeed is he who enjoys getting stabbed by sharp spines."};
descriptions["23149"]={cn:"外表狰狞，内里舒适。",en:"Comfortable on the inside, spiky on the outside."};
descriptions["23150"]={cn:"你也许会纳闷，这根从塞拉的创造物腹部里取出的杆子有什么用途。",en:"You may wonder what use anyone could have for this stake, retrieved from the abdomen of Sylargh\'s creations."};
descriptions["23151"]={cn:"腌制过的！",en:"It\'s pickled!"};
descriptions["23152"]={cn:"精英之选，倍加呵护。",en:"This cape will, without a doubt, assure your safety."};
descriptions["23153"]={cn:"在旺博戴上标志性的头带之前，他一直戴着这个护符。",en:"Before wearing his trademark bandana, Wambo proudly wore this amulet in public."};
descriptions["23154"]={cn:"You, wait! What area do you come from?",en:"You, wait! What area do you come from?"};
descriptions["23155"]={cn:"You, wait! What area do you come from?",en:"You, wait! What area do you come from?"};
descriptions["23156"]={cn:"It\'ll allow you to rob banks unnoticed.",en:"It\'ll allow you to rob banks unnoticed."};
descriptions["23157"]={cn:"It\'ll allow you to rob banks unnoticed.",en:"It\'ll allow you to rob banks unnoticed."};
descriptions["23158"]={cn:"There\'s nothing better than taking flight in style.",en:"There\'s nothing better than taking flight in style."};
descriptions["23159"]={cn:"There\'s nothing better than taking flight in style.",en:"There\'s nothing better than taking flight in style."};
descriptions["23160"]={cn:"Padded with kamas, this coat will keep you warm all winter!",en:"Padded with kamas, this coat will keep you warm all winter!"};
descriptions["23161"]={cn:"Padded with kamas, this coat will keep you warm all winter!",en:"Padded with kamas, this coat will keep you warm all winter!"};
descriptions["23162"]={cn:"These will give you the necessary self-confidence to face the monsters of Frigost.",en:"These will give you the necessary self-confidence to face the monsters of Frigost."};
descriptions["23163"]={cn:"These will give you the necessary self-confidence to face the monsters of Frigost.",en:"These will give you the necessary self-confidence to face the monsters of Frigost."};
descriptions["23164"]={cn:"The must-have kit for winter adventurers!",en:"The must-have kit for winter adventurers!"};
descriptions["23165"]={cn:"The must-have kit for winter adventurers!",en:"The must-have kit for winter adventurers!"};
descriptions["23166"]={cn:"It improves your dishes.",en:"It improves your dishes."};
descriptions["23167"]={cn:"Beauty can even be found in the middle of the desert.",en:"Beauty can even be found in the middle of the desert."};
descriptions["23168"]={cn:"Whether as a juice or in a salad, this delicate plant is known for its therapeutic virtues.",en:"Whether as a juice or in a salad, this delicate plant is known for its therapeutic virtues."};
descriptions["23169"]={cn:"Before being fished, he was buried deep in the sand, meditating, far from everything.",en:"Before being fished, he was buried deep in the sand, meditating, far from everything."};
descriptions["23170"]={cn:"原本用于保护伯爵的大钟，对于防御攻击也十分有效。",en:"This was actually designed to bear Count Harebourg\'s Clock Hand, but it turned out to be extremely effective against attacks."};
descriptions["23171"]={cn:"有了这柄指针，海尔伯格得以准确报时...",en:"Count Harebourg could use this to tell time with pinpoint accuracy."};
descriptions["23172"]={cn:"戴着这枚戒指的时候，想不冻僵手指也难。",en:"It\'s difficult for your fingers not to freeze off while wearing this ring."};
descriptions["23173"]={cn:"厚实的披氅，深受寒冰奇境猎人赞赏。",en:"This thick coat won\'t let the cold through. It\'s prized by Frigostian hunters for exactly that reason."};
descriptions["23174"]={cn:"戴着这对翅膀，直面危险挑战。虽然看起来像天使，但是穿起来难受极了！",en:"Fly into the face of danger with these wings. As angelic as they might seem, they\'re devilishly uncomfortable!"};
descriptions["23175"]={cn:"潮流选择，泡吧必备。即便是在漆黑之中，离着很远都看得到。",en:"A very trendy belt, ideal for clubbing. Thanks to its high visibility, this belt can be spotted from a distance, even when it\'s pitch black."};
descriptions["23176"]={cn:"由白鸦羽毛制成的稀有物品。获取它的唯一途径是击败黑鸦骑士...据说他死的时候羽毛会变成白色。",en:"A very rare item made of white crow feathers. The only way to get those is to kill a Black Crow... It\'s said that they turn white when they die."};
descriptions["23177"]={cn:"一个集齐轻柔，舒适，飘逸，厚实于一身的羽毛护肩，不正是你对敌中需要的重要装备吗！",en:"A soft, comfortable, floaty, three-ply, feathery neck-dress. Just what you need to wipe enemies out!"};
descriptions["23178"]={cn:"只有世界上最强的勇士才能染指的宝剑，以宝石镶嵌，闪烁着神秘的光辉。",en:"A beautifully-decorated black sword that only the hardest of the World\'s warriors can control."};
descriptions["23179"]={cn:"追踪飞鸟的最好办法是给它套个环！",en:"The best way to keep track of a bird is to ring it!"};
descriptions["23181"]={cn:"不要忘了放松一点头盔带...否则脱下来的时候就难了！",en:"Don\'t forget to unfasten the leather straps that hold this helmet to your head.... It might be a bit difficult to take off otherwise!"};
descriptions["23182"]={cn:"成为黑暗的主人，为自己的力量颤抖吧！",en:"Become the master of darkness and fear your own strength!"};
descriptions["23183"]={cn:"品质无懈可击。怪不得某骑士可以自由翱翔！",en:"These boots are in impeccable condition. It\'s not surprising for someone who did most of his traveling by air!"};
descriptions["23184"]={cn:"一根针，几根线以及从一只腐烂的乌鸦身上获得的羽毛若干...现在你拥有了十二世界中最时髦的披风！",en:"A needle, some thread and a few feathers taken from a decomposing Crobak... and now you have one of the most fashionable capes in the World of Twelve!"};
descriptions["23185"]={cn:"唯一能获取这件披风的方式是给绵矛革吹吹冷风，然后趁他哆嗦的时候偷走披风。",en:"The only known way to obtain this cloak is to give Magmog a cold and then whisk it off of his back at the most opportune moment."};
descriptions["23186"]={cn:"这些炙热的熔岩会给那些妄图佩戴这对肩甲的人一个难忘的教训。",en:"These hot coals will teach all those friends who use you as a shoulder to cry on a lesson."};
descriptions["23187"]={cn:"使用别人的脚穿越炽热的岩浆实在是太惬意了，看看它们还有很多其他的方便...我是说便利，便利快捷。",en:"It\'s always easier to walk across lava with someone else\'s feet on. These have the added benefit of looking grood... I mean good. And great. Great and good."};
descriptions["23188"]={cn:"光晕是什么？从没玩过！",en:"As the famous enraged Iop once cried out: Halo? What?! he\'s never even played it!"};
descriptions["23189"]={cn:"不停喷射着火焰。曾经属于一个强大的法师，在一场和绵矛革的战斗中损坏了。",en:"This wand bears an almighty flame. It used to belong to a powerful mage and got terribly broken during an epic fight with a Gobbalrog."};
descriptions["23191"]={cn:"一手当关，万夫莫开！",en:"With this on your arm, you can be sure of one thing... They shall not pass!"};
descriptions["23192"]={cn:"闪耀着光芒的头盔，十分有用。在寒冷的冬天，保证你双耳温暖。",en:"An incandescent helmet that is very good at keeping your ears warm during those chilly winters."};
descriptions["23193"]={cn:"即便仅仅是挂在楼下衣帽架上，依然让你觉得温暖舒适。",en:"A cloak that\'ll keep you warm, even when it\'s hanging on the coat rack downstairs."};
descriptions["23194"]={cn:"一脚踢飞所有拦路的绵球球。",en:"These Gobbalrog Boots will allow you to give a good boot to any flaming Gobbowl Ball coming your way."};
descriptions["23195"]={cn:"你看起来精神极了！皮肤过敏者慎用。同时也要当心屁股后面喷出火来。",en:"With this belt, you\'re sure to be full of beans! Not suitable for those with sensitive skin. Beware of backfire."};
descriptions["23196"]={cn:"夏天的烈日仍然不够火辣，这件胸甲给你再添一把火。",en:"As if the summer sun wasn\'t enough, here\'s a breastplate which aspires to be a radiator."};
descriptions["23197"]={cn:"也许你太肥了，没法飞起来，不过穿在身上真好看！",en:"You\'re too porky to actually leave the ground, but they look good on you!"};
descriptions["23198"]={cn:"戴上这顶帽子，你会变成全城知名的肥猪！",en:"Wrap this rindy hat around your head and you\'ll be the BIG PIG around town!"};
descriptions["23199"]={cn:"可爱的靴子，将你的敌人料理成沙拉。",en:"Some lovely pork knuckles to serve up on a bed of salad."};
descriptions["23200"]={cn:"穿着这件胸甲，你觉得安全舒适。褶皱和缝隙里都塞满了火腿肉。",en:"You\'ll feel safe and sound in this breastplate, whose chinks and cracks have been plugged up with cubes of ham."};
descriptions["23201"]={cn:"现在你可以在战斗中把双拳裹起来了！",en:"Now you can bandage up your fists for all those sweaty, porcine battles!"};
descriptions["23202"]={cn:"猪也会念经！",en:"Letting you have this necklace kind of feels like casting pearls before swine."};
descriptions["23205"]={cn:"猪头肉欧耶！",en:"Hamhead!"};
descriptions["23206"]={cn:"现在伟大的巨人就站在你的身旁，小不点。",en:"Now you have giants standing on your shoulders, dwarf."};
descriptions["23207"]={cn:"一件能够抵御任何扭曲的胸甲，同时它还具备特有的电台，只要你调频至\'N\'电台就可以每天都能听到有人在笑。",en:"Twist one of the wings on this thing and it\'ll tune you into Live \'n\' Lardy FM, the only radio station that will have you snorting with laughter all day long."};
descriptions["23208"]={cn:"我正踏着猪肉行走...哇哦酷！",en:"I\'m walking on bacon... Woooaaah!"};
descriptions["23209"]={cn:"魔族的这部分原来经常被用作门挡。后来有人觉得做成一顶帽子会更好。",en:"Intact, this half of a Shushu is usually used as a door stop. Then some people decided it would make a better hat."};
descriptions["23210"]={cn:"园丁必备，在播种之前可以用这种鞋子在地上挖坑。",en:"Ideal for gardeners, these boots are used to dig holes in the ground before planting seedlings in them."};
descriptions["23211"]={cn:"谁都希望一整天的心情都是暖暖的。这件胸甲能让你从内而外感到温暖，你值得拥有。",en:"Who hasn\'t dreamed of one day of warming the cockles of their heart? Now, with this breastplate that warms you up from the inside out, you can."};
descriptions["23212"]={cn:"谁都希望一整天的心情都是暖暖的。这件胸甲能让你从内而外感到温暖，你值得拥有。",en:"Who hasn\'t dreamed of one day of warming the cockles of their heart? Now, with this breastplate that warms you up from the inside out, you can."};
descriptions["23213"]={cn:"折磨人还是被人折磨，这是一个问题。",en:"Being deeply tormented by someone gives you strength, while tormenting someone deeply gives you courage."};
descriptions["23214"]={cn:"折磨人还是被人折磨，这是一个问题。",en:"Being deeply tormented by someone gives you strength, while tormenting someone deeply gives you courage."};
descriptions["23215"]={cn:"放轻松，统计表明仅仅只有 74.999% 的使用者发生了性格扭曲现象，请不用过于担心。",en:"Don\'t worry, this breastplate only provokes constant worrying in 74.999% of cases. Go ahead - put it on."};
descriptions["23217"]={cn:"据说装备了这个肩甲的人都已经成了受害者。你会是下一个吗？",en:"It is said that the protections that adorn these shoulder have already made victims of their own. Will you be next?"};
descriptions["23218"]={cn:"据说装备了这个肩甲的人都已经成了受害者。你会是下一个吗？",en:"It is said that the protections that adorn these shoulder have already made victims of their own. Will you be next?"};
descriptions["23219"]={cn:"折磨必定带来哭喊，你的靴子却异常安静。",en:"Each torment can be known by the cry that follows it. Your boots, though, are silent as the crypt."};
descriptions["23220"]={cn:"你一定是犯了错误才被要求穿上这件披风的。",en:"Wearing this cape isn\'t a sign of any great torment, but rather a multitude of little worries."};
descriptions["23221"]={cn:"我的灵魂充满了对力量的欲望...啊？是谁在说话？",en:"My spirit is tormented by my lust for power... said nobody, ever."};
descriptions["23222"]={cn:"啊...我的胃！好折磨！",en:"A stomach ache beats eternal torment any day."};
descriptions["23224"]={cn:"勒紧裤腰带，让我变得更坏。",en:"Strengthening the ties can only help you do more evil."};
descriptions["23228"]={cn:"深深地刺破你的皮肤，带来撕心裂肺的疼痛。",en:"Driven deeply into the skin, these spikes cause an incredible pain that isn\'t entirely disagreeable..."};
descriptions["23230"]={cn:"感觉有一只眼睛时刻盯着你的内心。",en:"You feel as if a legion of gazes are watching you and staring into your soul."};
descriptions["23231"]={cn:"根本难以直视。",en:"The first and last thing your enemies will see before they pass on."};
descriptions["23232"]={cn:"根本难以直视。",en:"The first and last thing your enemies will see before they pass on."};
descriptions["23233"]={cn:"You had to make terrible sacrifices to get this small tuft of hairs.",en:"You had to make terrible sacrifices to get this small tuft of hairs."};
descriptions["23234"]={cn:"一阵阵的耳边低语，让你瑟瑟发抖。",en:"Sheathe your body in a spine-tingling whisper."};
descriptions["23235"]={cn:"一阵阵的耳边低语，让你瑟瑟发抖。",en:"Sheathe your body in a spine-tingling whisper."};
descriptions["23236"]={cn:"你整天纳闷，究竟是谁在低声念叨着自己的名字。",en:"This headgear will have you turning in circles trying to figure out who\'s whispering your name."};
descriptions["23237"]={cn:"你整天纳闷，究竟是谁在低声念叨着自己的名字。",en:"This headgear will have you turning in circles trying to figure out who\'s whispering your name."};
descriptions["23238"]={cn:"长夜漫漫无人陪伴，最起码它可以陪你聊几句。",en:"If nobody else will whisper sweet nothings to you, at least your belt will."};
