descriptions["23375"]={cn:"在你的肩膀上安顿下来，让你不那么慌张。",en:"Resting gently on your shoulders, the hands serve as a big comfort when you\'re taking risks."};
descriptions["23376"]={cn:"在你的肩膀上安顿下来，让你不那么慌张。",en:"Resting gently on your shoulders, the hands serve as a big comfort when you\'re taking risks."};
descriptions["23377"]={cn:"恐惧之情溢于言表。",en:"Your fear shall be forever written upon your face."};
descriptions["23378"]={cn:"恐惧之情溢于言表。",en:"Your fear shall be forever written upon your face."};
descriptions["23379"]={cn:"一二三，跟你走。",en:"Once you tie them on, these giant paws will follow you anywhere you go."};
descriptions["23380"]={cn:"效果不错，使用前先看说明书。",en:"Quite handy for dealing with the undead."};
descriptions["23381"]={cn:"效果不错，使用前先看说明书。",en:"Quite handy for dealing with the undead."};
descriptions["23382"]={cn:"源自古老的家族，高品质的保证。",en:"This sword, created from unidentifiable bones is decorated with the forearm of a decrepit Borbat."};
descriptions["23383"]={cn:"这把刀藏在裤子口袋里，未免略大了一点吧。",en:"Even though it\'s heavy and a bit too thick for your pockets, this dagger is indispensable when it comes to cutting through bone."};
descriptions["23384"]={cn:"就好像握着有一双无形的手，想一想就觉得可怕。",en:"When you think about it, it\'s almost as if you\'re holding hands with the unfortunate former owner of these fingers."};
descriptions["23385"]={cn:"华而不实的东西。",en:"The purpose these chains serve is more decorative than functional."};
descriptions["23386"]={cn:"冬凉夏暖的东西。",en:"This shawl really keeps you warm in the summer - and cold in the winter."};
descriptions["23387"]={cn:"这件武器用来对付渣妈妈的试验品。",en:"This weapon is used to take apart Madame Enstein\'s experimental victims. Mostly it\'s used for \"detail work\"."};
descriptions["23388"]={cn:"紧紧绷绷的东西。",en:"Experiments work best when the subject is well restrained! And the team survives."};
descriptions["23389"]={cn:"僵尸舞会上的流行款，让硬朗的线条显出柔美的身姿。",en:"Very popular with our non-living friends, these rags allow for some pretty fluid movements, depending on the rigidity of the body in question."};
descriptions["23390"]={cn:"有着巨大的低胸领口，让刚站起来的尸体看起来更恐怖。",en:"A vest with a plunging neckline, guaranteed to look stunning on your newly reanimated corpse."};
descriptions["23391"]={cn:"维多利亚·爱因斯坦实验室的第一件作品，采用了最新的锁骨和肩胛骨制成。销量很差劲。",en:"One of Victoria-Franka\'s first experiments, using a clavicle and a scapula, which didn\'t quite turn out."};
descriptions["23392"]={cn:"但愿这双靴子和闻起来一样让人无法接近...",en:"Let\'s hope these boots are as solid as they are smelly..."};
descriptions["23393"]={cn:"但愿这双靴子和闻起来一样让人无法接近...",en:"Let\'s hope these boots are as solid as they are smelly..."};
descriptions["23394"]={cn:"巨魔杀手们视巨魔腰带为荣耀。",en:"Trool slayers normally wear their belts as a trophy. Well, the biggest ones do."};
descriptions["23395"]={cn:"巨魔杀手们视巨魔腰带为荣耀。",en:"Trool slayers normally wear their belts as a trophy. Well, the biggest ones do."};
descriptions["23396"]={cn:"戴着这件头盔，你会拥有很多乐趣！比如勾引一个女巨魔...",en:"With this scalp on your head, you\'re going to have so much fun! You might even manage to seduce a female Trool..."};
descriptions["23397"]={cn:"戴着这件头盔，你会拥有很多乐趣！比如勾引一个女巨魔...",en:"With this scalp on your head, you\'re going to have so much fun! You might even manage to seduce a female Trool..."};
descriptions["23398"]={cn:"巨魔穿起来显得高大威猛，你穿起来却猥琐得像绿皮。",en:"This cloak looked elegant on the Trool it came from, but it just makes you look like a deformed Bwork."};
descriptions["23399"]={cn:"用于储藏食物，以备不时之需。",en:"This belt used to be used to store snacks for those anxious moments."};
descriptions["23400"]={cn:"用于储藏食物，以备不时之需。",en:"This belt used to be used to store snacks for those anxious moments."};
descriptions["23401"]={cn:"有巨魔的大腿那么重，举起来就要耗尽你的所有力气。",en:"As heavy as an adult Trool\'s leg, this mace should get you sweating if nothing else."};
descriptions["23402"]={cn:"不错的战斗服装。但是没必要天天穿，除非你每天都在战斗。",en:"Troolish Shoulderguards are designed for use in battles of attrition. There\'s no need to wear them all day, every day, unless you see life as a constant battle."};
descriptions["23403"]={cn:"胜利源自努力。",en:"Victory is born of effort."};
descriptions["23404"]={cn:"授予巨魔学院的最终赢家。",en:"This ring is awarded to the winner of Trool Academy."};
descriptions["23405"]={cn:"授予巨魔学院的最终赢家。",en:"This mask is awarded to the winner of Trool Academy."};
descriptions["23406"]={cn:"坚实的防护源于超高的品质。这面盾足有半个巨魔的份量。只有力量够强的冒险者才举得起来。",en:"With great resistance comes great density. This shield weighs half a Trool, so it\'ll only protect you if you\'re really strong already."};
descriptions["23408"]={cn:"授予巨魔学院的赢家。然而，市场上马上就会出现无数的仿冒品。",en:"This weapon was the Trool Academy champion\'s lucky charm. When he became popular, the market was suddenly flooded with cheap rip-offs."};
descriptions["23409"]={cn:"仁者无敌。",en:"A loving heart is the truest wisdom."};
descriptions["23410"]={cn:"耐心是智慧之友。",en:"Patience is the companion of wisdom."};
descriptions["23411"]={cn:"能让你在海滩上像个果冻一样跳来跳去！",en:"These boots will have you hopping along the beach like a Jelly!"};
descriptions["23412"]={cn:"能让你在海滩上像个果冻一样跳来跳去！",en:"These boots will have you hopping along the beach like a Jelly!"};
descriptions["23413"]={cn:"面对沙滩，然后扑倒：这是炫耀披风的一种方式。",en:"Lie on your front on the beach: it\'s an adventurer sand-wich!"};
descriptions["23414"]={cn:"面对沙滩，然后扑倒：这是炫耀披风的一种方式。",en:"Lie on your front on the beach: it\'s an adventurer sand-wich!"};
descriptions["23415"]={cn:"这就是你的胸甲了...别以为没人看到你在胸前放了两个沙袋！",en:"This is the one for you... Don\'t think we haven\'t seen you making six-packs and womanly curves out of sand on the beach!"};
descriptions["23416"]={cn:"这就是你的胸甲了...别以为没人看到你在胸前放了两个沙袋！",en:"This is the one for you... Don\'t think we haven\'t seen you making six-packs and womanly curves out of sand on the beach!"};
descriptions["23417"]={cn:"由流沙制成。现在你可以不用洗手了。",en:"This ring is made of sand. A great reason to stop washing your hands."};
descriptions["23418"]={cn:"这样一来你可以轻松获得玩沙大赛！",en:"You could win the sandcastle competition in this any day!"};
descriptions["23419"]={cn:"这样一来你可以轻松获得玩沙大赛！",en:"You could win the sandcastle competition in this any day!"};
descriptions["23420"]={cn:"拿来在海滩边玩切西瓜游戏，不是切人游戏！",en:"For playing \"who can spear the ball first\" by the water\'s edge."};
descriptions["23421"]={cn:"里面的确藏了一朵玫瑰。只是不知道为什么，项链散发出沙子和小便的气味...一定很适合你。",en:"This delicate rose is made of a subtle blend of sand and urine. Suits you."};
descriptions["23422"]={cn:"曾经是米奇·软泡的收藏品。由松软的泡泡制成，只能抵挡沙尘...",en:"Despite being a favorite with Mitch Loosecannon, this board is made of foam and won\'t protect you from anything more than blowing sand."};
descriptions["23423"]={cn:"有这样的指环，全世界都变得真棒。",en:"With a ring like this, the world is your oyster!"};
descriptions["23424"]={cn:"现在你有地方存放重要文件了。只是文件会变得湿漉漉的。",en:"This belt has room for you to store your important documents, as long as you don\'t mind them getting all salty and wet."};
descriptions["23425"]={cn:"没有人见过颜色如此多彩的盾...",en:"This shield would have made a great palette for budding painters - if only it didn\'t let in so much water."};
descriptions["23426"]={cn:"再深的水现在你也能游上岸了！当然前提是你离岸很近。",en:"Now you can swim safely in even the deepest waters (as long as you stay near the top)."};
descriptions["23427"]={cn:"红花配绿叶，苍蝇叮烂肉。",en:"A man cannot learn wisdom by surrounding himself with ignorance."};
descriptions["23428"]={cn:"智慧可不仅仅是书本里的知识。",en:"\"Wisdom is not wisdom when it is derived from books alone.\""};
descriptions["23429"]={cn:"小巧可爱，力量强大。",en:"Tiny, sweet, gentle and cool. Tough, white, and oh so powerful!"};
descriptions["23430"]={cn:"小巧可爱，力量强大。",en:"Tiny, sweet, gentle and cool. Tough, white, and oh so powerful!"};
descriptions["23431"]={cn:"寒冰咕哩踏雪无痕的秘诀就是这双靴子...",en:"The Brrrblis trample the ice as they stampede, but the island\'s temperature instantly freezes the water after they have passed, creating pretty white ripples."};
descriptions["23432"]={cn:"寒冰咕哩踏雪无痕的秘诀就是这双靴子...",en:"The Brrrblis trample the ice as they stampede, but the island\'s temperature instantly freezes the water after they have passed, creating pretty white ripples."};
descriptions["23433"]={cn:"这么冷的天气带着这条腰带没事吗？你可没有寒冰咕哩那么厚的脂肪！",en:"It\'s not a good idea to tighten your belt in such freezing conditions! Better go out on a full stomach: after all, you\'re not endowed with an extra layer of fat like a Brrrbli."};
descriptions["23434"]={cn:"这么冷的天气带着这条腰带没事吗？你可没有寒冰咕哩那么厚的脂肪！",en:"It\'s not a good idea to tighten your belt in such freezing conditions! Better go out on a full stomach: after all, you\'re not endowed with an extra layer of fat like a Brrrbli."};
descriptions["23435"]={cn:"保护你的正面和背面免受严寒，其他部位受到伤害没人管得着...",en:"This breastplate shields your front and behind, so feel free to take some hits for the others!"};
descriptions["23436"]={cn:"保暖性能极好，即便面临暴风雪也无所谓畏惧。",en:"These shoulder pads are incredibly frost-resistant and are very useful when plunging headlong into a blizzard, as you do."};
descriptions["23437"]={cn:"保暖性能极好，即便面临暴风雪也无所谓畏惧。",en:"These shoulder pads are incredibly frost-resistant and are very useful when plunging headlong into a blizzard, as you do."};
descriptions["23438"]={cn:"轻轻一戳就能刺穿冰面！",en:"The slightest stroke of this sword is enough to break the ice!"};
descriptions["23439"]={cn:"用来碎冰的最好选择。只是实在太冻手了...",en:"This hammer would be the ultimate ice-breaker, if it weren\'t so cold to handle."};
descriptions["23440"]={cn:"饭冰冰最爱的指环，但愿她还带得上。",en:"This ring is the centerpiece of Brrrbley Spears\'s collection and would be worth its weight in gold if only the market wasn\'t frozen."};
descriptions["23441"]={cn:"饭冰冰时常在寒冰大陆上，眺望子嗣们到处乱窜...",en:"In the midst of the icicles rearing up all over the Ice Floe, Brrrbley Spears watches over her children."};
descriptions["23442"]={cn:"饭冰冰随身携带的匕首，",en:"This dagger is as lethal as the ice floe that Brrrbley Spears has chosen to make her home!"};
descriptions["23443"]={cn:"深处寒冰奇境，你得穿得暖些，特别是脑袋。",en:"You\'ve got to wrap up warmly on Frigost Island, especially your head. You wouldn\'t want to end up with Iop brain-freeze, would you?"};
descriptions["23444"]={cn:"即便是寒冰咕哩面对这把法杖也要发疯抓狂！从此之后你能够击倒的小怪物就会不计其数！",en:"This wand will make all Brrrblis completely crazy about you!\nYou\'ll have little monsters coming at you by the bucket load!"};
descriptions["23445"]={cn:"显然，你需要更多悟性。",en:"Wisdom comes with experience, which you still lack."};
descriptions["23446"]={cn:"由于法杖本身制作时使用了大量的雪原木以至于它看起来十分的光滑，然而它最大的特点是能够将敌人一分为二。",en:"This staff is made principally of Frozen Wood, which lends it a shiny and fragile appearance. One of its special features is its ability to split enemies in two!"};
descriptions["23447"]={cn:"当你望向它的双眼，你会觉得它想要攻击你。",en:"When you look it in the eyes, you get the feeling it\'s going to attack."};
descriptions["23448"]={cn:"当你望向它的双眼，你会觉得它想要攻击你。",en:"When you look it in the eyes, you get the feeling it\'s going to attack."};
descriptions["23449"]={cn:"绑紧一点，要不然他会试图逃跑",en:"Tighten it properly, otherwise it may try to escape."};
descriptions["23450"]={cn:"绑紧一点，要不然他会试图逃跑",en:"Tighten it properly, otherwise it may try to escape."};
descriptions["23451"]={cn:"这靴子真的可以在地上踏出痕迹，或是在你对手的脸上",en:"These boots are really practically to make marks on the ground... or on your opponent\'s face."};
descriptions["23452"]={cn:"这靴子真的可以在地上踏出痕迹，或是在你对手的脸上",en:"These boots are really practically to make marks on the ground... or on your opponent\'s face."};
descriptions["23453"]={cn:"这件斗篷散发的怪味之野性...举世无双。",en:"Nothing\'s wilder than the odor of this cloak."};
descriptions["23454"]={cn:"只要看到这个帽子，你的敌人在攻击你之前会多考虑一下",en:"Upon seeing this hat, your opponents will think twice before attacking you."};
descriptions["23455"]={cn:"只要看到这个帽子，你的敌人在攻击你之前会多考虑一下",en:"Upon seeing this hat, your opponents will think twice before attacking you."};
descriptions["23456"]={cn:"盘丝怪结的网再大，也能用这个掸子轻松掸除。",en:"Great for sweeping up even the biggest Arachnoshima webs."};
descriptions["23457"]={cn:"盘丝怪结的网再大，也能用这个掸子轻松掸除。",en:"Great for sweeping up even the biggest Arachnoshima webs."};
descriptions["23458"]={cn:"挺起胸膛，上战场粉碎你的敌人。",en:"Dive into a fight chest-first to crush your enemies."};
descriptions["23459"]={cn:"这个锋利的头饰，能让你的对手望而生畏。",en:"Look down on your opponents thanks to this sharp headgear."};
descriptions["23460"]={cn:"一个聚集了豆芙怒气的护符",en:"An amulet made from concentrated Tofu anger."};
descriptions["23461"]={cn:"你没办法再找到比这更好的靴子。如果你这样做，他们就会攻击你",en:"You\'ll never find better boots than these. If you claim otherwise, they\'ll attack you."};
descriptions["23462"]={cn:"你没办法再找到比这更好的靴子。如果你这样做，他们就会攻击你",en:"You\'ll never find better boots than these. If you claim otherwise, they\'ll attack you."};
descriptions["23463"]={cn:"你必须要很有胆量才能把手指套入这指环",en:"You need to be brave to dare put your finger in such a wild ring."};
descriptions["23464"]={cn:"冲向你的敌人 - 不给他们任何机会。",en:"Rush at your enemy - they won\'t stand a chance."};
descriptions["23465"]={cn:"狂怒豆芙的狂怒全部凝聚到了这副坚固的胸甲之中。",en:"The entire fury of an Enraged Tofu is concentrated into this tough armor."};
descriptions["23466"]={cn:"给你的箭失杀人不眨眼的本能，来自大自然的力量。",en:"Give your arrows a murderous instinct, drawn from the forces of nature."};
descriptions["23467"]={cn:"有这样时髦的装备，很难保证你的人身安全阿",en:"With such a swanky piece of kit, it\'s difficult to keep your head on your shoulders!"};
descriptions["23468"]={cn:"这野性的指环毫无约束感。",en:"This wild-natured ring knows no restraint."};
descriptions["23469"]={cn:"只是看它一眼，你就会想要拚命的去触摸它。",en:"One look at this wood and you\'ll be dying to touch it for yourself."};
descriptions["23470"]={cn:"It seems a Lenald came by here...",en:"It seems a Lenald came by here..."};
descriptions["23471"]={cn:"This mushroom was already quite pungent; once dried, it\'s literally stifling.",en:"This mushroom was already quite pungent; once dried, it\'s literally stifling."};
descriptions["23472"]={cn:"With this model specimen, you can surely produce the best canvases of your generation.",en:"With this model specimen, you can surely produce the best canvases of your generation."};
descriptions["23473"]={cn:"Wear this cape and you\'ll feel refreshed; it is known for having energizing virtues, thanks to its red blubbles.",en:"Wear this cape and you\'ll feel refreshed; it is known for having energizing virtues, thanks to its red blubbles."};
descriptions["23474"]={cn:"It\'s sweet and will soothe your mouth.",en:"It\'s sweet and will soothe your mouth."};
descriptions["23475"]={cn:"防火装备。好似当头被浇了一盆凉水。",en:"This helmet is essential fire-fighting equipment. It will put a damper on any fiery spirits nearby."};
descriptions["23476"]={cn:"This headgear makes you looked annoyed and irritable. Speaking of which, why are Puddlies so nasty?",en:"This headgear makes you looked annoyed and irritable. Speaking of which, why are Puddlies so nasty?"};
descriptions["23477"]={cn:"Its difficulty in spelling its own name have already caused it quite a lot of trouble.",en:"Its difficulty in spelling its own name have already caused it quite a lot of trouble."};
descriptions["23478"]={cn:"Why not?",en:"Why not?"};
descriptions["23479"]={cn:"This is a very effective combustible, so make sure you always have some on you when venturing: you never know when you\'ll need a fire.",en:"This is a very effective combustible, so make sure you always have some on you when venturing: you never know when you\'ll need a fire."};
descriptions["23480"]={cn:"It has a unique shine that gives it all its charm.",en:"It has a unique shine that gives it all its charm."};
descriptions["23481"]={cn:"让羽毛飞一会儿！",en:"You\'ll be able to make the feathers fly with this ring!"};
descriptions["23482"]={cn:"让羽毛飞一会儿！",en:"You\'ll be able to make the feathers fly with this ring!"};
descriptions["23483"]={cn:"有效防止腰痛。也许还有别的效果？穿上之后才知道。",en:"This belt is supposed to improve back trouble. Or is that the other way round? You won\'t know until you try it on!"};
descriptions["23484"]={cn:"有效防止腰痛。也许还有别的效果？穿上之后才知道。",en:"This belt is supposed to improve back trouble. Or is that the other way round? You won\'t know until you try it on!"};
descriptions["23485"]={cn:"每走一步都伴着一声乌鸦惨叫。光靠声音就可以把敌人吓走了，不战而屈人之兵。",en:"These Croboots emit a Crow squawk with every step you take. You can make the enemy flee just by warning them of your imminent arrival."};
descriptions["23486"]={cn:"每走一步都伴着一声乌鸦惨叫。光靠声音就可以把敌人吓走了，不战而屈人之兵。",en:"These Croboots emit a Crow squawk with every step you take. You can make the enemy flee just by warning them of your imminent arrival."};
descriptions["23487"]={cn:"一件可以拿来在地下酒馆里炫耀的胸甲。",en:"A feathery thing that you can take great pleasure in showing off in the most squalid tavern in town."};
descriptions["23488"]={cn:"好比带了一只鸟在脖子上。它可不会保护你。",en:"Wearing this amulet is a bit like having a great big bird around your neck, which is why it won\'t really protect you from baddies."};
descriptions["23489"]={cn:"好比带了一只鸟在脖子上。它可不会保护你。",en:"Wearing this amulet is a bit like having a great big bird around your neck, which is why it won\'t really protect you from baddies."};
descriptions["23490"]={cn:"长长的鸦羽，不断刺激你发笑。",en:"These epaulettes are so feathery they\'ll almost make you gaga!"};
descriptions["23491"]={cn:"据说这副眼镜能让你鸟瞰一切。但愿这只鸟不是近视眼！",en:"They say that this monocle allows you to see everything with a bird\'s-eye view. Here\'s hoping the bird in question wasn\'t short-sighted!"};
descriptions["23492"]={cn:"让敌人眼冒星星。",en:"Use this shield to defend yourself and you\'ll leave your adversaries seeing stars!"};
descriptions["23493"]={cn:"为了让护肩看上去有质感，所以采用金属作为制作材料。",en:"These epaulettes are made of a metal that was worked extensively in order to give it that rusted copper look."};
descriptions["23494"]={cn:"可以戴在任何鸦人上。",en:"The bits and pieces can be used by any Kraw."};
descriptions["23495"]={cn:"这是卡波克的第一批样品。",en:"These boots were part of Kabrok\'s first prototypes."};
descriptions["23496"]={cn:"你将会是下一个幸运之星。",en:"A whack from this sword will hit your enemies like a bolt from the blue."};
descriptions["23497"]={cn:"仿佛置身于云朵之中...事实上...你置身于...星辰...",en:"It\'s like having your head in the clouds... except that... it\'s in the...  stars..."};
descriptions["23498"]={cn:"鞋面上布满了蓝色星星，带你进入梦想之地。",en:"You\'re sure to be happy with these boots. They\'re covered in blue stars and foot the bill perfectly for walking on air!"};
descriptions["23499"]={cn:"别想着自己也能像鸟那样在天上飞...后果可不只是掉几根毛而已...",en:"Don\'t bother trying a flying raid like you\'ve seen the birds do - you risk leaving more than just a few feathers behind..."};
descriptions["23500"]={cn:"别想着自己也能像鸟那样在天上飞...后果可不只是掉几根毛而已...",en:"Don\'t bother trying a flying raid like you\'ve seen the birds do - you risk leaving more than just a few feathers behind..."};
descriptions["23501"]={cn:"穿上以后能让你回避一些普通的反击。",en:"These shoulderguards let you dodge regular counterattacks when attacking merchant convoys."};
descriptions["23502"]={cn:"穿上以后能让你回避一些普通的反击。",en:"These shoulderguards let you dodge regular counterattacks when attacking merchant convoys."};
descriptions["23503"]={cn:"年轻的流氓鸦到了一定的年纪后就会用它们的翅膀飞走并在科尔巴岛上建立起自己的巢穴。",en:"As soon as young Raskaws reach the age of adventure, they use their wings to fly away and establish their very own encampment in the Lands of Kelba."};
descriptions["23504"]={cn:"年轻的流氓鸦到了一定的年纪后就会用它们的翅膀飞走并在科尔巴岛上建立起自己的巢穴。",en:"As soon as young Raskaws reach the age of adventure, they use their wings to fly away and establish their very own encampment in the Lands of Kelba."};
descriptions["23505"]={cn:"你看上去就像克罗伯当地人一样。",en:"You look like you came straight out of the Kreublo."};
descriptions["23506"]={cn:"令人垂涎的绷带，用来抚慰冒险者充满鲜血的手。",en:"A very sought after bandage, for soothing the murderous hands of young raiders."};
descriptions["23507"]={cn:"令人垂涎的绷带，用来抚慰冒险者充满鲜血的手。",en:"A very sought after bandage, for soothing the murderous hands of young raiders."};
descriptions["23508"]={cn:"生成于世间万物，可以轻易的划过克罗伯的羽毛。",en:"This dagger is made of anything and everything, and can easily slip between the feathers of an intrepid Krueblo youth."};
descriptions["23509"]={cn:"克罗伯村的年轻人最喜欢的饰物，这腰带让他们的羽毛显得很漂亮。",en:"The Krawsh embellishes the outfits of Kreublo youths, and really shows off their plumage too."};
descriptions["23510"]={cn:"鸦人传说尖酸长枪是大酋长带过来的。在月圆之时它会与你的灵魂立下契约。",en:"The Raskaw legend says that this lance was brought to the Lands of Kelba by the original Grand Orrok. It will reinforce your link to the sacred spirit on contact, on nights where the full moon is partly hidden by clouds."};
descriptions["23511"]={cn:"这是一位村庄长老穿戴的头饰，用来证明他不是普通的村民。",en:"This headgear is worn by the village chief in order to distinguish himself from his peers."};
descriptions["23512"]={cn:"有了这块缠布，你已经是最森林中最酷炫的了。",en:"With this loincloth, you can have the best-looking assets in the woods."};
descriptions["23513"]={cn:"在山上你必须穿鞋子，这会让你保住小命！",en:"In the mountains, you have to keep on your feet - it will help keep you from falling to your death!"};
descriptions["23514"]={cn:"克罗伯年轻人通常拥有更加松软的羽毛。当然其实差别并不明显。",en:"Kreublo youths generally have softer and silkier plumage than the adults. The difference is really pretty subtle though."};
descriptions["23515"]={cn:"这个护符给予克罗伯村年轻人酋长般的勇气，让他们能穿过科尔巴岛。",en:"This Amulet is offered to young members of Kreublos winging their way through the Lands of Kelba to give them the courage of the Orrok."};
descriptions["23516"]={cn:"和祖先之间的羁绊让他们变得更加强大。",en:"The link the Raskaw people have with their ancestors makes all the more powerful."};
descriptions["23518"]={cn:"连结至酋长之魂的美丽羽毛，或者至少是个高级赝品。",en:"Magnificent wings linked to the Orrok spirit. Or at least a very good imitation!"};
descriptions["23519"]={cn:"脏兮兮的项链，说不定会为你带来疾病。别被吓到了！",en:"This dirty necklace might just give you some nasty diseases. Don\'t get pooped out!"};
descriptions["23521"]={cn:"脏兮兮的项链，说不定会为你带来疾病。别被吓到了！",en:"This dirty necklace might just give you some nasty diseases. Don\'t get pooped out!"};
descriptions["23522"]={cn:"当心你的手指！啊，已经迟了...",en:"Watch where you put that finger! Oops, too late..."};
descriptions["23523"]={cn:"当心你的手指！啊，已经迟了...",en:"Watch where you put that finger! Oops, too late..."};
descriptions["23524"]={cn:"闻到老鼠味道了？",en:"Smell a rat...? Oh..."};
descriptions["23525"]={cn:"闻到老鼠味道了？",en:"Smell a rat...? Oh..."};
descriptions["23526"]={cn:"你知道吗，你现在看起来就像是刚从下水道爬出来一样。",en:"You look like you just crawled out of a sewer, you know."};
descriptions["23527"]={cn:"鼠家族好不容易东拼西凑，缝了件衣服...",en:"This breastplate was cobbled together using patches of fabric and armor from all the members of the Rat family."};
descriptions["23528"]={cn:"鼠家族好不容易东拼西凑，缝了件衣服...",en:"This breastplate was cobbled together using patches of fabric and armor from all the members of the Rat family."};
descriptions["23529"]={cn:"现在你知道为什么路上那些幸运猫在你经过的时候始终在吞口水了。",en:"Now you know why those Ecaflips were licking their lips when you walked past them a moment ago."};
descriptions["23530"]={cn:"上一个主人弄丢了这把魔杖，因为他后来一个手指都不剩了。",en:"Apparently this wand\'s last owner dropped it because he didn\'t have any fingers left."};
descriptions["23531"]={cn:"和挺起的肚腩说再见吧！",en:"The instructions on the packet say that, if you hit your enemy in just the right spot, some of his body parts will pop right out! But where...? Now, that\'s the question."};
descriptions["23532"]={cn:"围在胸前就是围兜兜了，闻着味道不错哦！",en:"Whip this cloak round to the front and you can use it as a bib. To be honest, the smell coming off it is making you drool already..."};
descriptions["23533"]={cn:"即使做成了标本，生前的口臭仍旧在一阵阵地散发出来。戴着它上街的话，请务必远离人群。",en:"This rat may be stuffed, but the halitosis it suffered in life has become stronger than ever in death. When you\'re walking around town, you part crowds without even trying!"};
descriptions["23534"]={cn:"鼠太后传下来的戒指，不知道哪位姑娘有幸能戴上。",en:"This ring used to belong to Ratical\'s mother. Apparently, whoever\'s wearing it is the life and soul of the party!"};
descriptions["23535"]={cn:"用鼠王及其党羽的肢体制成。多数敢用的人根本不知道护盾的原料。",en:"This shield is made up of all the body parts that were left over after one of Ratical\'s riotous parties. If you can bear to carry it, you probably don\'t realize that\'s what it\'s made of."};
descriptions["23536"]={cn:"别怕，不是虫子，看起来像而已...其实，是老鼠尾巴...",en:"Oh, don\'t worry, it\'s not a worm! It\'s just a hairless, creepy, squidgy rat tail. Watch out for splinters!"};
descriptions["23537"]={cn:"当侯媛夫人发明出这种工具来清理落叶后，斯拉斯拉德先生已经迫不及待的借来用作清理他敌人的遗骸了，一个也不能落下。",en:"When Lady Gardenmore invented this tool for gathering dead leaves into piles, Sir Slayalday couldn\'t wait to borrow it to do the same thing with enemies\' corpses. Each to their own."};
descriptions["23538"]={cn:"这条护符的作用是保证你能笔直向前飞...当然，没人敢保证你不撞到墙...",en:"This amulet\'s goal is to keep you on the straight and narrow... Although, judging by the direction you\'ve taken so far, I\'m not sure going straight on is ideal..."};
descriptions["23539"]={cn:"仿佛踩着敌人的尸体前进。晚上，它们会发出令人胆寒的声音。",en:"These boots give you the strange sensation of walking on your opponents\' remains. At night, especially, they make some very unnerving sounds."};
descriptions["23540"]={cn:"仿佛踩着敌人的尸体前进。晚上，它们会发出令人胆寒的声音。",en:"These boots give you the strange sensation of walking on your opponents\' remains. At night, especially, they make some very unnerving sounds."};
descriptions["23541"]={cn:"太阳下山后，腰带上的狼毛愈发的柔软贴身。",en:"The hairs on this very soft belt become strangely clingy when the sun goes down."};
descriptions["23542"]={cn:"太阳下山后，腰带上的狼毛愈发的柔软贴身。",en:"The hairs on this very soft belt become strangely clingy when the sun goes down."};
descriptions["23543"]={cn:"狼会因为各种小虫子搅扰无法入眠。多亏了这顶帽子，现在你也有了同样的权利。",en:"Boowolves fall pray to countless little nocturnal parasites. Thanks to this hat, you too can benefit from the extra waking hours they add to your day."};
descriptions["23544"]={cn:"狼会因为各种小虫子搅扰无法入眠。多亏了这顶帽子，现在你也有了同样的权利。",en:"Boowolves fall pray to countless little nocturnal parasites. Thanks to this hat, you too can benefit from the extra waking hours they add to your day."};
descriptions["23545"]={cn:"没有比肩膀上戴着两个狼爪更可靠的了。然而你有没有觉得在夜晚，狼爪好像总会变长一点...？",en:"What could be more reassuring than having two enormous Boowolf paws on your shoulders? Though have you noticed how the claws always feel like they\'re getting longer at night...?"};
descriptions["23546"]={cn:"当心半夜里被咬一口。",en:"Careful with this amulet. It might just bite you in the middle of the night."};
descriptions["23547"]={cn:"当心半夜里被咬一口。",en:"Careful with this amulet. It might just bite you in the middle of the night."};
descriptions["23548"]={cn:"狼毛加厚，防风防雨。虽然不如神秘的满月护盾结实，抵挡小家伙们的攻击还是绰绰有余。",en:"This shield has been weatherproofed using Boowolf hairs. It\'s not as efficient as the mythical Foolmoun, but it provides pretty good protection against droplets."};
descriptions["23549"]={cn:"自从这件胸甲上市之后，人们发现了一种崭新的战斗方式...长毛攻击。",en:"Since this breastplate arrived on the market, a new fighting technique has been seen on the battlefield. It\'s known as \'tufting.\'"};
descriptions["23550"]={cn:"是的，狼也需要带头绳，你问这是为什么？所有人都需要展示他温柔的一面不是吗！",en:"Yes, Boowolwes also wear Strings, so what? Everyone is entitled to their share of femininity!"};
descriptions["23551"]={cn:"满月在手，世界我有。\n恩，虽然只有一点点。",en:"They say he\'s got the whole World in his hands, but it looks like you\'ve got the moon! \nWell, a bit of it, at least."};
descriptions["23552"]={cn:"孩子们都喜欢这双靴子...夜里迈出的每一步都散发出皎洁的月光。",en:"All the kids LOVE these boots - they\'re the kind that light up with every step you take. We know, we know, you used to have a pair..."};
descriptions["23553"]={cn:"带你飞向月球，才怪。",en:"Unfortunately it won\'t fly you to the moon, nor let you play among the stars."};
descriptions["23554"]={cn:"一个人走夜路时记得带着这枚护符。",en:"This lucky amulet will protect you from those uneasy midnight encounters."};
descriptions["23555"]={cn:"在森林里穿会显得很可怕，能展现你隐藏的狂野一面。",en:"This mask can be pretty terrifying\nif worn in the forestand will really bring out your wild side."};
descriptions["23556"]={cn:"畜生禁用。",en:"Not for brutes."};
descriptions["23557"]={cn:"标签上写着“即使有摩擦也依然柔顺。”\n不幸的是，冒险者通常没有这特征。",en:"The label reads \"Gentle, even when rubbed the wrong way.\"\nA characteristic you often don\'t find with adventurers, unfortunately."};
descriptions["23558"]={cn:"标签上写着“即使有摩擦也依然柔顺。”\n不幸的是，冒险者通常没有这特征。",en:"The label reads \"Gentle, even when rubbed the wrong way.\"\nA characteristic you often don\'t find with adventurers, unfortunately."};
descriptions["23559"]={cn:"如果你已经戴上它，强烈建议你取下来。我们已经警告过你了...",en:"Once you\'ve put this ring on, it\'s highly recommended that you take it off again. You have been warned..."};
descriptions["23560"]={cn:"如果你已经戴上它，强烈建议你取下来。我们已经警告过你了...",en:"Once you\'ve put this ring on, it\'s highly recommended that you take it off again. You have been warned..."};
descriptions["23561"]={cn:"闪闪发亮的腰带。在黑夜中行走时，让你的龙鸟清晰可见。",en:"This belt can also be used as a hi-vis band to make your Dragoturkey visible to other path users on dark nights."};
descriptions["23562"]={cn:"闪闪发亮的腰带。在黑夜中行走时，让你的龙鸟清晰可见。",en:"This belt can also be used as a hi-vis band to make your Dragoturkey visible to other path users on dark nights."};
descriptions["23563"]={cn:"眼睛比肚子还大。",en:"Your eyes are bigger than your belly."};
descriptions["23564"]={cn:"里里外外毛毛茸茸的。",en:"Hairy inside and out."};
descriptions["23565"]={cn:"里里外外毛毛茸茸的。",en:"Hairy inside and out."};
descriptions["23566"]={cn:"如果你的背上不能有一双额外的眼睛，至少你可以把它们戴在头上。",en:"If you can\'t have an extra set of eyes on your back, you can at least have them on your head."};
descriptions["23567"]={cn:"想拿起法杖仔细端详的蠢货最终都会受辐射变成三眼怪物。谨慎选择你的目标。",en:"Whatever numbskull takes this cudgel in the face is likely to sprout a third eye on a stalk. Choose your targets well."};
descriptions["23568"]={cn:"挥舞时闪烁着七彩的火花。也许对于环境并不好，但是漂亮极了！",en:"When used, this wand releases pretty sparks in all different colors. It\'s not very good for the planet, but it\'s so cute!"};
descriptions["23569"]={cn:"黑寡妇有一大堆这种靴子。碰巧盗贼时尚杂志推荐它们为本季流行款！",en:"The Black Widow has tons of these boots to spare, which is just as well, because Rogue magazine says they\'re in this season!"};
descriptions["23570"]={cn:"由黑寡妇亲自一针一线、辛辛苦苦地缝制完成。投石机也对它无可奈何。还等什么，赶快穿上吧。",en:"This cloak was woven thread by thread by the meticulous Black Widow herself. A Catapulted Crackler would have no chance against it, so I don\'t know why you\'re so quick to put it on your back."};
descriptions["23571"]={cn:"估计她再也不需要这玩意儿了，现在她可是个寡妇。",en:"I suppose she doesn\'t need it any more, now she\'s a widow."};
descriptions["23572"]={cn:"黑寡妇诱惑了一只盘丝蜘蛛，然后掰下了它的一条腿来制造她的设计品，行为十分卑劣。",en:"The Black Widow bamboozled an Arachnee Embroiderer and nabbed one of its hands for her own dastardly designs."};
descriptions["23573"]={cn:"你不是有健全的双腿么？站起来，向前走！",en:"Boots with a built-in rhythm system to make sure you step to the beat! That part in the pantomime might be yours at last!"};
descriptions["23574"]={cn:"你看上去像个发着萤光的伞菇！",en:"From above, you look like a radioactive toadstool!"};
descriptions["23575"]={cn:"看起来像南瓜节糖果，可是无法食用。",en:"This amulet may look like an Al Howin\'s Treat, but that\'s no reason to eat it."};
descriptions["23578"]={cn:"在脖子上围一个缩水的布丁头饰，会带给你力量和智慧。实际上这恶心极了。",en:"Wearing a shrunken puddly head around your neck will bring you strength and wisdom. It is disgusting, though."};
descriptions["23579"]={cn:"在脖子上围一个缩水的布丁头饰，会带给你力量和智慧。实际上这恶心极了。",en:"Wearing a shrunken puddly head around your neck will bring you strength and wisdom. It is disgusting, though."};
descriptions["23580"]={cn:"当你仔细端详这个神秘的戒指的时候，会看到有一道绿影闪过，留下歪歪扭扭的痕迹和一堆泡泡。",en:"Sometimes, if you look deep into the pearl on this mystical ring, you will see a greenish light glowing at the bottom, followed by some frantic movements and a few bubbles."};
descriptions["23581"]={cn:"当你仔细端详这个神秘的戒指的时候，会看到有一道绿影闪过，留下歪歪扭扭的痕迹和一堆泡泡。",en:"Sometimes, if you look deep into the pearl on this mystical ring, you will see a greenish light glowing at the bottom, followed by some frantic movements and a few bubbles."};
descriptions["23582"]={cn:"虽然看起来很有型，但是想穿着它们奔跑还要适应一段时间。",en:"These Getas are excellent for improving your posture, but you\'re going to need to practice if you ever hope to be able to run in them."};
descriptions["23583"]={cn:"虽然看起来很有型，但是想穿着它们奔跑还要适应一段时间。",en:"These Getas are excellent for improving your posture, but you\'re going to need to practice if you ever hope to be able to run in them."};
descriptions["23584"]={cn:"戴上之前摇一摇...小布丁都藏在里面。",en:"Give this hat a shake before you put it on - Dinky Puddlies tend to hide inside it."};
descriptions["23585"]={cn:"贵族游戏，但是五分钟后你就觉得无聊了，你开始想像你的下一根棍子是什么样的。",en:"Fun for the novelty, but after five minutes it gets boring and you start dreaming of your next club."};
descriptions["23586"]={cn:"贵族游戏，但是五分钟后你就觉得无聊了，你开始想像你的下一根棍子是什么样的。",en:"Fun for the novelty, but after five minutes it gets boring and you start dreaming of your next club."};
descriptions["23587"]={cn:"布丁草团对于纸球和肥皂泡有着出色的防御效果。",en:"Puddly straw offers excellent protection against paper balls and soap bubbles."};
descriptions["23588"]={cn:"手持这柄铲子，清除屋子前恶心的布丁。",en:"Always have this shovel on hand to clear the path in front of your house of nasty puddles."};
descriptions["23589"]={cn:"This headgear makes you looked annoyed and irritable. Speaking of which, why are Puddlies so nasty?",en:"This headgear makes you looked annoyed and irritable. Speaking of which, why are Puddlies so nasty?"};
descriptions["23590"]={cn:"妥善保管这件披风。我的朋友有一件，但是他把披风忘在了阳光下，融化了。",en:"Be very careful with this cloak. A friend of mine had one, but he left it out in the sun and it vanished."};
descriptions["23591"]={cn:"因为你刚装在肩膀上的滑梯，你头上的虱子们决定选你做本月最佳市民。它们正在申请建个游泳池。",en:"Just so you know, your head lice have voted you Citizen of the Month for the slides you installed on your shoulders, and are now petitioning for a swimming pool."};
descriptions["23592"]={cn:"敌人会吓得泪流成河。",en:"The only sword you need to make your enemies cry you a river."};
descriptions["23593"]={cn:"那是...？我想是的...！瀑布！！！",en:"Is that a...? I think it is...! WATERFAAAALL!!!"};
descriptions["23594"]={cn:"据说这条腰带曾经属于一个有名的布丁...但是没有人记得住它的名字。",en:"It\'s said that this belt used to belong to a famous Puddly... but everyone\'s forgotten his name."};
descriptions["23595"]={cn:"奇怪的披风，丑陋的外表是它力量的源泉。越脏，就越有用。",en:"This strange cape draws all its power from its dilapidated appearance. The dirtier it is, the more use it will be to you."};
descriptions["23596"]={cn:"兽人必须死！",en:"Death to Bworks!"};
descriptions["23597"]={cn:"What talent...",en:"What talent..."};
descriptions["23598"]={cn:"This stretchy cord is great for catapulting all sorts of projectiles, provided they\'re not too heavy, that is.",en:"This stretchy cord is great for catapulting all sorts of projectiles, provided they\'re not too heavy, that is."};
descriptions["23599"]={cn:"黑珍珠船长收藏的锋利黑色尖头，也许是他过往生涯的纪念物...",en:"A sharp, dark tip that the Captain of the Dark Hurl kept safe. Maybe a souvenir of his mortal life..."};
descriptions["23600"]={cn:"穿起披风，你看起来就和树皮一样粗糙。",en:"If you want to look gnarly, snap this cape up!"};
descriptions["23601"]={cn:"穿起披风，你看起来就和树皮一样粗糙。",en:"If you want to look gnarly, snap this cape up!"};
descriptions["23602"]={cn:"这只树皮覆盖的戒指将成为你的战斗利器。",en:"This bark-covered ring will help you take revenge on your enemies."};
descriptions["23603"]={cn:"这只树皮覆盖的戒指将成为你的战斗利器。",en:"This bark-covered ring will help you take revenge on your enemies."};
descriptions["23604"]={cn:"穿上它，告诉全世界你有多强力！",en:"With these on your shoulders, you\'ll be able to show the whole World what you\'re made of!"};
descriptions["23605"]={cn:"穿上它，告诉全世界你有多强力！",en:"With these on your shoulders, you\'ll be able to show the whole World what you\'re made of!"};
descriptions["23606"]={cn:"由干燥的树精灵木制成的拖鞋，十分舒适。木质的内衬，充满粘液，每一步都如履平地。",en:"These thongs, made from dried Treechnid wood, are surprisingly comfortable: the wooden sole is filled with sap that cushions your each and every step!"};
descriptions["23607"]={cn:"这件胸甲有些僵硬。为了回归自然，这是值得的代价。",en:"Yes, this breastplate might be a little stiff, but that\'s the price you have to pay if you want to be at one with nature."};
descriptions["23608"]={cn:"这件胸甲有些僵硬。为了回归自然，这是值得的代价。",en:"Yes, this breastplate might be a little stiff, but that\'s the price you have to pay if you want to be at one with nature."};
descriptions["23609"]={cn:"放暑假时，这条软木腰带折叠起来可以当安全带用。",en:"This wooden belt was designed to double up as a lifebelt during the summer holidays."};
descriptions["23610"]={cn:"你只需要一只卷笔刀，就能让这把匕首变成令敌人胆寒的武器。",en:"All you need to make this weapon a fearsome battle companion is a decent pencil sharpener."};
descriptions["23611"]={cn:"用一块木头去砍伐另一块木头...你不觉得很讽刺吗？",en:"Chopping wood with wood... Isn\'t that ironic? Dontcha think?"};
descriptions["23612"]={cn:"如果护符坏了，那是因为乌鸦整天在树皮上又啄又扯的缘故。",en:"If this amulet is in bad condition, blame the Crobaks that spend their days pecking and tearing at Treechnids\' bark."};
descriptions["23613"]={cn:"戒指不错...从客观角度来讲。你戴起来漂亮极了。我可不想要，可是你戴确实不错...",en:"This ring is nice... I mean, in an understated way. It looks good on you. I wouldn\'t wear one myself, but you know..."};
descriptions["23614"]={cn:"但愿远古树精的树皮比它的牙齿坚硬。",en:"Let\'s hope the Ancestral Treechnid\'s bark is stronger than his bite."};
descriptions["23615"]={cn:"戴上之后，你就明白什么叫做敲木头，祈求好运不溜走了。",en:"That\'s what you call knocking on wood!"};
descriptions["23616"]={cn:"由树木和金属制成。让敌人尝尝你的厉害吧。",en:"This pendant is made from wood and metal fused together. That will really show your enemies what you\'re made of."};
descriptions["23617"]={cn:"这把法杖由鲜活的树精根部制成。注意，这些树根会背叛他们的主人。",en:"This staff is made from living Treechnid roots. Be warned, these do have an annoying tendency to turn against their masters."};
descriptions["23618"]={cn:"你想得到穿兽人的靴子走一英里的感觉，但是你想不到会留下多少汗水和疼痛...",en:"You\'ve always wanted to walk a mile in a Bwork\'s shoes, but you didn\'t think of the half-inch of scum and sweat that would be left behind... Squelch! but you didn\'t think of the half-inch of scum and sweat that would be left behind... Squelch! Urgh!"};
descriptions["23619"]={cn:"你想得到穿兽人的靴子走一英里的感觉，但是你想不到会留下多少汗水和疼痛...",en:"You\'ve always wanted to walk a mile in a Bwork\'s shoes, but you didn\'t think of the half-inch of scum and sweat that would be left behind... Squelch! but you didn\'t think of the half-inch of scum and sweat that would be left behind... Squelch! Urgh!"};
descriptions["23620"]={cn:"兽人都爱棕色。他们用野性绵球绒毛制成了这件披风。好吧，这只是个谣言。你绝对不想知道这件披风是用什么做的。",en:"It\'s said that the leather used in making this cape was tanned using the secretions of a Wild Gobball. This is only a rumor though. The truth is far worse."};
descriptions["23621"]={cn:"兽人都爱棕色。他们用野性绵球绒毛制成了这件披风。好吧，这只是个谣言。你绝对不想知道这件披风是用什么做的。",en:"It\'s said that the leather used in making this cape was tanned using the secretions of a Wild Gobball. This is only a rumor though. The truth is far worse."};
descriptions["23622"]={cn:"据说兽人从来不脱衣服和头盔，也不会洗衣服和头盔，更不会洗澡...",en:"Some say the Bworks never take their armor off and never wash it. They never wash themselves either, for that matter."};
descriptions["23623"]={cn:"据说兽人从来不脱衣服和头盔，也不会洗衣服和头盔，更不会洗澡...",en:"Some say the Bworks never take their armor off and never wash it. They never wash themselves either, for that matter."};
descriptions["23624"]={cn:"尽管做工粗糙，但是很结实。如果不是臭气熏天的话，战斗中十分好用。",en:"Despite the primitive craftsmanship, this breastplate seems pretty solid. It would be perfect for combat, were it not for the odor of Bwork wafting from literally every surface."};
descriptions["23625"]={cn:"简易好用的剑。用来敲打比砍削更实在。只是手柄上很粘，不知道是什么东西...",en:"Simple and effective, this blade is designed more to crush than cut. The only thing that makes you doubt its combat-worthiness is the sticky handle..."};
descriptions["23626"]={cn:"简易好用的剑。用来敲打比砍削更实在。只是手柄上很粘，不知道是什么东西...",en:"Simple and effective, this blade is designed more to crush than cut. The only thing that makes you doubt its combat-worthiness is the sticky handle..."};
descriptions["23627"]={cn:"你永远不知道这帮兽人是怎么制造盾牌的...常人难以理解。",en:"You\'ve turned it this way and that, and still cannot understand how they got the iron around the wooden center. Unless they somehow inserted the wooden center into the iron? You may never know..."};
descriptions["23628"]={cn:"别被名字吓到了。所谓的缠绕物只是一条腰带...据说当年由史上最大的绿皮佩戴。当那个绿皮正常的时候，腰带看起来也很正常。然而，当绿皮狂性大发的时候，这条腰带能在身体膨胀N倍的情况下保持裤子依然贴身不掉落。",en:"Don\'t be fooled by the highfalutin name. It\'s said this \"cincture\" is actually the repurposed toe ring of what must be the biggest Bwork in history. As we all know, as the dimensions of a Bwork increase by a factor of n, Bwork surface area increases by n squared. Much more skin to catch the sun. At the same time, Bwork volumetric mass increases by n cubed. Much, much more fat to soak up the sun and insulate. Which all amounts to a really fat, really sweaty Bwork with a really sweaty toe ring. Lots."};
descriptions["23629"]={cn:"虽然用兽人传统原料制成，但是做工精细，外观整洁...似乎对于兽人的大脑袋来说，不太好套进去啊...",en:"This Bwork amulet is fairly disturbing. Other than the delicateness which it was created with compared to normal Bwork products, it\'s its cleanliness which is most shocking! Oh! But of course. The cord is much too short to go around the head and ears of a Bwork."};
descriptions["23630"]={cn:"简洁有用，结实耐操。索克的最爱。",en:"Solid, simple, effective. Thork likes massive epaulettes. That way, he looks like he\'s more than just a Bwork."};
descriptions["23631"]={cn:"由兽人的胡须制成。不起眼，但是很有用。",en:"Thork\'s only apparently useless accessory, the amulet is made of the beard of an ancient Bwork named Nad\'Lug. In actuality, it\'s really powerful."};
descriptions["23632"]={cn:"靴子上的尖刺给兽人探险者留下了深刻印象。很明显这双靴子踢过很多屁股...",en:"The spikes on Thork\'s boots had always impressed his fellow Bwork Explorers. It\'s plain to see they\'ve been used to kick a few butts..."};
descriptions["23633"]={cn:"时间在你掌握之中！想睡多久睡多久！",en:"Now you have The Watch, time is in your hands! You can be as late as you like!"};
descriptions["23634"]={cn:"调校完美的强弓，射出的箭矢直击隐蔽敌人。怪物如惊弓之鸟，四散奔逃。",en:"Yamato\'s Rope has made more than one monster\'s heart beat a little faster. A finely tuned weapon, it can direct arrows to even the most well-hidden targets."};
descriptions["23635"]={cn:"制造这件披风只有一个目的：它必须连着数天都能让主人清醒着。",en:"This cape was made with just one goal in mind: It had to be able to keep its owner awake for a few days running."};
descriptions["23636"]={cn:"现在，绵球的荣耀由你来承担了。",en:"Now, the weight of the wool is on your shoulders. Ancient Gobball Hunter proverb"};
descriptions["23637"]={cn:"现在，绵球的荣耀由你来承担了。",en:"Now, the weight of the wool is on your shoulders. Ancient Gobball Hunter proverb"};
descriptions["23638"]={cn:"牢牢套在手指上，完全取不下来。",en:"This ring will wear your fingers to the bone."};
descriptions["23639"]={cn:"牢牢套在手指上，完全取不下来。",en:"This ring will wear your fingers to the bone."};
descriptions["23640"]={cn:"冬天，也许会有喵喵躲到你头上取暖。",en:"One thing is certain: if you come across a Bow Meow, it will curl up for a nice nap in your warm headgear."};
descriptions["23641"]={cn:"冬天，也许会有喵喵躲到你头上取暖。",en:"One thing is certain: if you come across a Bow Meow, it will curl up for a nice nap in your warm headgear."};
descriptions["23642"]={cn:"穿着这件胸甲，你可以去冰山岛转一圈。当然并不保证你可以活着回来。",en:"It\'s been said that with this breastplate, you could stroll around Frigost almost completely naked. Note the word \"survive\" was not mentioned."};
descriptions["23643"]={cn:"拿起这把战锤，你脑子里只剩一个念头：战！",en:"With this hammer you have one and only one desire: smash, smash and SMASH!"};
descriptions["23644"]={cn:"拿起这把战锤，你脑子里只剩一个念头：战！",en:"With this hammer you have one and only one desire: smash, smash and SMASH!"};
descriptions["23645"]={cn:"散发着一股恶臭。",en:"This belt is as warm as it is odorous."};
descriptions["23646"]={cn:"聪明的人永远不会惹这柄法杖的主人。",en:"The wise man admits he knows nothing. He also doesn\'t mess with someone wielding this staff."};
descriptions["23647"]={cn:"可以用作洗衣板，十分便利。",en:"When you\'re not wearing this cape, you can use it as a very effective scouring pad."};
descriptions["23648"]={cn:"野性绵球的一块骨头，魔力有待证明。",en:"Although it\'s a real Wild Gobball bone, its magic virtues remain to be proven."};
descriptions["23649"]={cn:"踢别人屁股的上佳选择。",en:"The wilder the Great Gobball was, the more getting kicked in the butt with these boots will hurt."};
descriptions["23650"]={cn:"能射出带有臭气的强力弓矢。",en:"Can shoot odoriferous and, frankly, disgusting arrows."};
descriptions["23651"]={cn:"巨大的宝剑，能将体型巨大的敌人切成汉堡肉。千万别跳瑞士八字舞来庆祝...你的队友会感谢你的。",en:"This enormous sword is efficient at turning even the largest enemies into hamburger meat. Just make sure you don\'t do that swishy figure-of-eight thing to celebrate - your teammates will thank you."};
descriptions["23652"]={cn:"由奥金纳克残骸以及其他残渣制成。因为长期由恐怖的古尔洛拥有，道奇成为了荒凉的象征。",en:"The Daudgee is made from Ouginak remains and various other refuse. Worn by Gourlo the Terrible for a long time, the Daudgee is the image of desolation."};
descriptions["23653"]={cn:"面向贵族阶层的法杖。装备起来，即便是在战斗中，你也觉得自己好像变成了贵族。",en:"This staff was made with the upper classes in mind. Equip it and you\'ll feel like a nobleman, even in the middle of a bloody battle."};
descriptions["23654"]={cn:"如果戒指发出喘息声，不用紧张。因为有一个饱受折磨的海盗灵魂寄居其上。",en:"If your finger starts breathing by itself when you put this ring on, relax: it\'s just the soul of a tortured pirate who\'s been trapped inside for several decades."};
descriptions["23655"]={cn:"如果戒指发出喘息声，不用紧张。因为有一个饱受折磨的海盗灵魂寄居其上。",en:"If your finger starts breathing by itself when you put this ring on, relax: it\'s just the soul of a tortured pirate who\'s been trapped inside for several decades."};
descriptions["23656"]={cn:"100% 幽灵纤维制成。世代相传的好靴子！",en:"These boots are made of 100% authentic Ghostof fabric. They\'re gonna live forever!"};
descriptions["23657"]={cn:"100% 幽灵纤维制成。世代相传的好靴子！",en:"These boots are made of 100% authentic Ghostof fabric. They\'re gonna live forever!"};
descriptions["23658"]={cn:"不是我夸你，但是你戴这顶帽子确实很帅。",en:"No need to toot your own horn, but you look very respecta-bull with this hat on. Toot toot!"};
descriptions["23659"]={cn:"不是我夸你，但是你戴这顶帽子确实很帅。",en:"No need to toot your own horn, but you look very respecta-bull with this hat on."};
descriptions["23660"]={cn:"你说什么？你昨天刚见过？他们已经死了20多年了...！",en:"What do you mean, you saw them just yesterday? They\'ve been dead for twenty yeeeaaars...!"};
descriptions["23661"]={cn:"一根旧绳索制成的水手腰带。外观普普通通，但是结实耐用。",en:"A sailor belt made from a length of old rope. It\'s not fancy, but it\'ll do the job."};
descriptions["23662"]={cn:"一根旧绳索制成的水手腰带。外观普普通通，但是结实耐用。",en:"A sailor belt made from a length of old rope. It\'s not fancy, but it\'ll do the job."};
descriptions["23663"]={cn:"这件胸甲实在太寒碜了，用来假装在海难中幸存的船员倒是很合适，有船走过记得呼救。",en:"This breastplate is so battered and worn that you could easily pretend to be a shipwreck survivor and cadge a lift off a friendly ship."};
descriptions["23664"]={cn:"这把铲子有很多宝藏猎人拥趸，因为他们坚信铲子能为他们找到宝藏。实际上只能挖到没洗的短裤。信仰是盲目的。",en:"Many Enutrofs swear loyalty to this shovel because they think it will help them find treasure. All it ever seems to dig up is dirty underpants, though. Is faith really this blind?"};
descriptions["23665"]={cn:"蕴含了高科技的盾牌，能从捕获的所有灵魂中吸取精华，转化为自身的防御力。硬度与粘度俱佳！",en:"This high-tech shield draws its resistance from all the souls it has captured. Its hardiness is matched only by its stickiness!"};
descriptions["23666"]={cn:"如果一阵风吹过，披风会变成绿色并剧烈抖动。",en:"Just so you know, if you ever feel some trapped wind letting loose, this cloak will turn green and start vibrating violently."};
descriptions["23667"]={cn:"内置的通风系统能24小时排汗。",en:"These epaulettes\' inbuilt ventilation system will have you churning out stale, piratey air 24/7."};
descriptions["23668"]={cn:"有点紧。老实说，如果你能够穿上一件幽灵缠绕的衣服，你显然不会因为外观这种细节问题而沮丧。",en:"This breastplate is a little too tight, but to be honest, if you\'re happy wearing a garment made of old Ghostofs, you obviously don\'t care much about your appearance."};
descriptions["23669"]={cn:"当锤子敲击大地的时候，散发出一股令人作呕的气味。你最好学着远程战斗，而且要快！",en:"When this hammer hits the ground, a nauseating stench fills the vicinity. It\'s in your best interest to learn how to fight from a distance, and fast!"};
descriptions["23670"]={cn:"镶嵌着一个骷髅头，让你看起来像追风少年。",en:"Embellished with a skull to give you the bad-boy look you\'ve been coveting so."};
descriptions["23671"]={cn:"带有扣带，防止水手在甲板上摔个狗啃泥。",en:"These boots have a good grip on them to stop the seamen falling flat on their faces."};
descriptions["23672"]={cn:"打牌时出老千的优秀道具。",en:"This belt offers a handy spot for pirates to store their aces when playing cards (everyone knows their sleeves were long ago ripped off by raging captains, crocodiles, or the wear and tear of sea life)."};
descriptions["23673"]={cn:"如果你被冰山困住了，这件披风可以提供助你脱困的热气流。",en:"This cloak has thermal elements which will help you out if you ever get stuck on a glacier."};
descriptions["23674"]={cn:"如果你想不出什么好主意，你可以拿这对护肩往墙上扔，或者往敌人身上扔。",en:"If you are short of ideas, you could always use these epaulettes to smash up walls as well as your enemies."};
descriptions["23675"]={cn:"第一眼看上去好像轻如羽毛。实际上重得跟砖块一样。使劲！",en:"At first glance, this breastplate seems as light as a feather. In reality it\'s as heavy as a sack of bricks. Make sure you buff up before attempting to put it on!"};
descriptions["23676"]={cn:"自动发射箭矢，根本不需要费一点力气。",en:"Don\'t lift a finger, the arrow will launch itself!"};
descriptions["23677"]={cn:"用来攻击比防御好多了。",en:"This shield is better at biffing and bashing than blocking."};
descriptions["23678"]={cn:"一触碰到其他剑，就会发出令人毛骨悚然的刺耳笑声。",en:"As soon as this sword crosses with another it emits a piercing, metallic-sounding cackle."};
descriptions["23679"]={cn:"据说胸针的制造者是著名的铁匠布林加。是的，就是他制造了神的武器。",en:"People say the famous Blacksmith Boulgur made this brooch. Yes, the guy who created weapons for the gods."};
descriptions["23680"]={cn:"如果你捡到这条腰带，那么恭喜你：这条腰带曾经属于一个世上最强的英雄。他留着胡须，魅力无法抵挡。",en:"If you happen to have this belt on your hips, you\'re in luck: it used to belong to the strongest and most seductive bearded hero of all time."};
descriptions["23681"]={cn:"It streams tears whenever you deprive it of dessert.",en:"It streams tears whenever you deprive it of dessert."};
descriptions["23682"]={cn:"They can be found in all of Amakna\'s auditoriums.",en:"They can be found in all of Amakna\'s auditoriums."};
descriptions["23683"]={cn:"Even during an adventure, you can find the comfort of a warm night at the inn thanks to this fern leaf, which is incredibly soft an cozy!",en:"Even during an adventure, you can find the comfort of a warm night at the inn thanks to this fern leaf, which is incredibly soft an cozy!"};
descriptions["23684"]={cn:"There\'s a legend about mermaids who sing in the ocean at night. Actually, it\'s algae hissing when lit up by the moonlight.",en:"There\'s a legend about mermaids who sing in the ocean at night. Actually, it\'s algae hissing when lit up by the moonlight."};
descriptions["23685"]={cn:"Be careful, because if you rub two twigs together, this thing\'ll light up like a torch.",en:"Be careful, because if you rub two twigs together, this thing\'ll light up like a torch."};
descriptions["23686"]={cn:"It\'ll help you get through any difficult moment.",en:"It\'ll help you get through any difficult moment."};
descriptions["23687"]={cn:"Vive la revolution!",en:"Vive la revolution!"};
descriptions["23688"]={cn:"Although this fish is fresh from the water, you now desire nothing more than to throw it back in there.",en:"Although this fish is fresh from the water, you now desire nothing more than to throw it back in there."};
descriptions["23689"]={cn:"“一个戒指，哦哒。两个戒指，哦哒哒！”\n诺斯特拉诺斯 - 随想录",en:"\"One ring, biff kapow. Two rings, biff bang kablooey!\"\nNostralanus - Thoughts"};
descriptions["23690"]={cn:"“一个戒指，哦哒。两个戒指，哦哒哒！”\n诺斯特拉诺斯 - 随想录",en:"\"One ring, biff kapow. Two rings, biff bang kablooey!\"\nNostralanus - Thoughts"};
descriptions["23691"]={cn:"全能的腰带。好吧，几乎全能。哦哒哒哒！",en:"This belt does everything. Well, almost. Kapow sock whack!"};
descriptions["23692"]={cn:"全能的腰带。好吧，几乎全能。哦哒哒哒！",en:"This belt does everything. Well, almost. Kapow sock whack!"};
descriptions["23693"]={cn:"哦哒哒哒哒哒哒哒哒！！！",en:"A lightly perfumed breastplate which is wonderfully attractive to hungry Gobballs in the area."};
descriptions["23694"]={cn:"哦哒哒哒哒哒哒哒哒！！！",en:"A lightly perfumed breastplate which is wonderfully attractive to hungry Gobballs in the area."};
descriptions["23695"]={cn:"轻如羽翼。你只需要等梦想照进现实的一天就好了...哦哒哒哒...",en:"This helmet is as light as a feather. All you have to do is wait for the wind to get up to turn your dreams of flying into reality... Crash Bang Wallop *stars*... Maybe not."};
descriptions["23696"]={cn:"看来是我高估你了。哦哒，哦哒哒哒。",en:"Hitting with your bare hands is overrated. Awkkkkkk ooooff cr-r-a-a-ck clunk-eth."};
descriptions["23697"]={cn:"看来是我高估你了。哦哒，哦哒哒哒。",en:"Hitting with your bare hands is overrated. Awkkkkkk ooooff cr-r-a-a-ck clunk-eth."};
descriptions["23698"]={cn:"啊啊啊！你最终还是决定把戒指还给他！",en:"Aaaah! You\'ve finally decided to let him slip his ring over your finger!"};
descriptions["23699"]={cn:"始终让你的双脚保持清爽舒适！",en:"Your feet will always feel fresh and moist in these!"};
descriptions["23700"]={cn:"紧急情况下，用这个戒指内含的油脂来烧敌人吧！",en:"In case of emergency, use the oil given off by this ring to fry your enemies!"};
descriptions["23701"]={cn:"饥饿的眼睛凝视着你。",en:"With this amulet around your neck you\'re bound to get more than a few glances from hungry eyes."};
descriptions["23702"]={cn:"柔软如嫩羊排。",en:"As tender as Gobball steak."};
descriptions["23703"]={cn:"你是我见过最勇敢的人！",en:"A gutsy breastplate if ever I saw one!"};
descriptions["23704"]={cn:"不可与皮肤直接接触。",en:"Never put this amulet in direct contact with your skin."};
descriptions["23705"]={cn:"如果听到饱嗝声，要知道并不一定是从你的胃发出来的。",en:"For once, if you hear gurgling, it\'s probably not coming from your stomach."};
descriptions["23706"]={cn:"据说能提供完美的伪装，但是好像你已经隐形了。不要在意细节！",en:"I\'d tell you that this cloak is said to provide the perfect camouflage, but you appear to have disappeared. Never mind!"};
descriptions["23707"]={cn:"由树叶纤维制成。",en:"This ring is made of several leaf fibers."};
descriptions["23708"]={cn:"很明显是从树上硬扒下来的...",en:"It looks like it was nicked while it was asleep in the woods."};
descriptions["23709"]={cn:"仔细看！据说它会向空气中释放剧毒气体。幸运的是，现在好像不会了。",en:"Get an eyeful of this amulet! True to its origins, it would love to continue to spray its pestilent odor over all and sundry. Fortunately for you, it seems to be all pooped out."};
descriptions["23710"]={cn:"仔细看！据说它会向空气中释放剧毒气体。幸运的是，现在好像不会了。",en:"Get an eyeful of this amulet! True to its origins, it would love to continue to spray its pestilent odor over all and sundry. Fortunately for you, it seems to be all pooped out."};
descriptions["23711"]={cn:"记得定期停下来给鞋子浇点水，它们会报答你的！",en:"Remember to stop and water your boots at regular intervals, they\'ll thank you for it!"};
descriptions["23712"]={cn:"记得定期停下来给鞋子浇点水，它们会报答你的！",en:"Remember to stop and water your boots at regular intervals, they\'ll thank you for it!"};
descriptions["23713"]={cn:"戴上这顶帽子，人们会觉得你像被钓起来的鱼。",en:"With this hat on your head, people will think something fishy\'s up."};
descriptions["23714"]={cn:"戴上这顶帽子，人们会觉得你像被钓起来的鱼。",en:"With this hat on your head, people will think something fishy\'s up."};
descriptions["23715"]={cn:"送礼佳品...太臭了，会熏死人。",en:"This is the type of ring you should never offer to your partner - it smells so bad that they\'re likely to pass out if they put it on."};
descriptions["23716"]={cn:"这戒指被诅咒了。据说造成了很多水手丧生，他们的船长在出海时就戴着它。",en:"This ring is jinxed. They say it led to the deaths of many sailors when their captain, remembering all the old wives\' tales, slipped it onto his finger when far out at sea."};
descriptions["23717"]={cn:"这戒指被诅咒了。据说造成了很多水手丧生，他们的船长在出海时就戴着它。",en:"This ring is jinxed. They say it led to the deaths of many sailors when their captain, remembering all the old wives\' tales, slipped it onto his finger when far out at sea."};
descriptions["23718"]={cn:"无论你多么努力地去洗，你都无法去除那股要命的鱼腥味。",en:"Scrub it as hard as you like, you\'ll never be able to get rid of that delightful Snapper smell."};
descriptions["23719"]={cn:"无论暴晒多久，总是湿漉漉的。沙漠旅行必备。",en:"This amulet is always wet, no matter how many times you try to dry it off. It\'s just what you need for a trip to the desert!"};
descriptions["23720"]={cn:"这柄和旗鱼嘴一样锋利宝剑，能教会你鱼群战斗的艺术！",en:"With this sword, shaped like a Zordfish beak, you will master the art of Snapper combat!"};
descriptions["23721"]={cn:"虽然又轻又薄，但是还是别再太阳底下穿...一股子鱼腥味。",en:"Although it\'s airy and light, it is best not to wear this cloak in the sun - it absolutely humdings of fish."};
descriptions["23722"]={cn:"萨弗基亚人相信这根项链能带来好运，因为它在夜晚发出闪闪的红光。当然，这也意味着小偷和杀手在晚上也能毫不费力地找到你。",en:"Sufokians say that this amulet is lucky because it glows in the night. Then again, that does mean that thieves and assassins will never have trouble spotting you."};
descriptions["23724"]={cn:"这肩甲的设计初衷是让穿戴着能在水里飘浮...那么一秒钟，然后你就石沉大海了。",en:"These epaulettes are designed to make you float when you\'re in water... Unfortunately, it only works for a second before you sink like a stone."};
descriptions["23725"]={cn:"象牙做的靴子？谁想出来的？开除。",en:"Boots made of ivory? Okay, who had this idea? He\'s fired."};
descriptions["23726"]={cn:"古朴雅致的披风，每个人都想摸一下。这太糟糕了！",en:"A cape so white and pristine that everyone you meet will be tempted to take a tinkle on it. Too bad."};
descriptions["23727"]={cn:"萨弗基亚人相信这根项链能带来好运，因为它在夜晚发出闪闪的红光。当然，这也意味着小偷和杀手在晚上也能毫不费力地找到你。",en:"Sufokians say that this amulet is lucky because it glows in the night. Then again, that does mean that thieves and assassins will never have trouble spotting you."};
descriptions["23728"]={cn:"我们的目标是，没有蛀牙！",en:"You\'ll want to keep this wand in good condition. If you ever need it in an emergency, the last thing you\'ll want is some sort of blockage."};
descriptions["23729"]={cn:"哒哒哒哒...",en:"Da do tron tron tron, da do tron tron ~"};
descriptions["23730"]={cn:"似乎能让拥有者微笑应对任何情况。如果你确定想拥有它，你得确保一天刷两次牙！",en:"It seems this terrible helmet enables its wearer to smile in all situations.  If you want one of these, you\'re going to have to make sure you brush your teeth twice a day!"};
descriptions["23731"]={cn:"似乎能让拥有者微笑应对任何情况。如果你确定想拥有它，你得确保一天刷两次牙！",en:"It seems this terrible helmet enables its wearer to smile in all situations.  If you want one of these, you\'re going to have to make sure you brush your teeth twice a day!"};
descriptions["23732"]={cn:"土匪们增加了他们腰包的空间，以免抢劫的时候装不下。",en:"The Riktus have reinforced the purse attachment to make sure they don\'t get beaten at their own game."};
descriptions["23733"]={cn:"土匪们增加了他们腰包的空间，以免抢劫的时候装不下。",en:"The Riktus have reinforced the purse attachment to make sure they don\'t get beaten at their own game."};
descriptions["23734"]={cn:"穿着总比什么都不穿好，至少这件破烂袍子能让你备受周围人的瞩目，和嘲笑。",en:"It might not be much good for anything else, but at least this deformed toga has the marvelous ability to make the people around you burst spontaneously into laughter."};
descriptions["23735"]={cn:"穿着总比什么都不穿好，至少这件破烂袍子能让你备受周围人的瞩目，和嘲笑。",en:"It might not be much good for anything else, but at least this deformed toga has the marvelous ability to make the people around you burst spontaneously into laughter."};
descriptions["23736"]={cn:"不服？来战。",en:"Let the standards of war be drawn!"};
descriptions["23737"]={cn:"盾牌上狰狞的笑脸很容易吸引敌人注意力。",en:"The daunting smile on this shield will conveniently distract your adversary."};
descriptions["23738"]={cn:"盾牌上狰狞的笑脸很容易吸引敌人注意力。",en:"The daunting smile on this shield will conveniently distract your adversary."};
descriptions["23739"]={cn:"小心使用。能轻易引起地震，赶走入侵者。",en:"Go careful when using this bow. It can cause earthquakes that shoot off the Richter."};
descriptions["23740"]={cn:"挖的宝藏越多，你笑得越开心。",en:"Your smile grows wider with every piece of treasure you unearth!"};
descriptions["23741"]={cn:"奖励给最勇敢的土匪。",en:"This beautiful sword is awarded to the most courageous Riktus."};
descriptions["23742"]={cn:"阿玛克纳土匪是大土匪家族中最活跃的一派，这件胸甲是他们狡猾的证明。",en:"The Amakna Riktus are the most robust of the widespread Riktus family and this breastplate makes that very clear."};
descriptions["23743"]={cn:"阿玛克纳土匪是大土匪家族中最活跃的一派，这件胸甲是他们狡猾的证明。",en:"The Amakna Riktus are the most robust of the widespread Riktus family and this breastplate makes that very clear."};
descriptions["23744"]={cn:"邦塔土匪是大土匪家族中最顽固的一派，这件胸甲也显示出了正统坚固的风格。",en:"The Bonta Riktus are as hard as nails and the most resistant of the widespread Riktus family. This breastplate follows suit."};
descriptions["23745"]={cn:"邦塔土匪是大土匪家族中最顽固的一派，这件胸甲也显示出了正统坚固的风格。",en:"The Bonta Riktus are as hard as nails and the most resistant of the widespread Riktus family. This breastplate follows suit."};
descriptions["23746"]={cn:"布拉克玛土匪以他们超人的力量闻名于世，所以不要低估这件胸甲可以造成的伤害。",en:"The Brakmar Riktus are known for their super-human force, so don\'t underestimate the damage that this breastplate can inflict."};
descriptions["23747"]={cn:"布拉克玛土匪以他们超人的力量闻名于世，所以不要低估这件胸甲可以造成的伤害。",en:"The Brakmar Riktus are known for their super-human force, so don\'t underestimate the damage that this breastplate can inflict."};
descriptions["23748"]={cn:"萨弗基亚土匪以打游击闻名，这并不意味着他们害怕正面进攻！",en:"The Sufokia Riktus are primarily renowned for their robbing and running, but they\'re not afraid of attacking if they have to!"};
descriptions["23749"]={cn:"萨弗基亚土匪以打游击闻名，这并不意味着他们害怕正面进攻！",en:"The Sufokia Riktus are primarily renowned for their robbing and running, but they\'re not afraid of attacking if they have to!"};
descriptions["23750"]={cn:"百搭的就是极好的！",en:"An amulet that goes with all your outfits...! There is a god!"};
descriptions["23751"]={cn:"用于铲除野草。由于功效出众，慢慢变成了军用品。",en:"This garden shovel is used to cut the rhizomes of weeds. It\'s also an excellent weapon when it comes to cutting other things."};
descriptions["23752"]={cn:"毁灭一切！",en:"It\'s going to destroy everything!"};
descriptions["23753"]={cn:"能让佩戴者的存在感归零的戒指。不是隐形哦，真的不是隐形哦！",en:"This ring\'s strength lies in its ability to make its wearer completely transparent. You do understand we\'re not talking about invisibility here, don\'t you?"};
descriptions["23754"]={cn:"Quite a rare vapor that is highly prized by alchemists.",en:"Quite a rare vapor that is highly prized by alchemists."};
descriptions["23755"]={cn:"感受今年滋滋节的愤怒吧！",en:"This item was all the rage at the Plastronboory Festival this year."};
descriptions["23756"]={cn:"感受今年滋滋节的愤怒吧！",en:"This item was all the rage at the Plastronboory Festival this year."};
descriptions["23757"]={cn:"因为护符上的蚊眼，使你腹背受敌。",en:"Thanks to the Moskito eye adorning this amulet, you can anticipate oncoming danger from all four directions."};
descriptions["23758"]={cn:"因为护符上的蚊眼，使你腹背受敌。",en:"Thanks to the Moskito eye adorning this amulet, you can anticipate oncoming danger from all four directions."};
descriptions["23759"]={cn:"我有个朋友曾经戴过同一款式的帽子。有一天，他勇敢地向一群呆呱挑战。从那以后，我再也没有听到过他的消息...",en:"I had a friend who used to wear a hat like this all the time. But one day, he ventured into an Oafish Toad colony, and was never heard from again..."};
descriptions["23760"]={cn:"我有个朋友曾经戴过同一款式的帽子。有一天，他勇敢地向一群呆呱挑战。从那以后，我再也没有听到过他的消息...",en:"I had a friend who used to wear a hat like this all the time. But one day, he ventured into an Oafish Toad colony, and was never heard from again..."};
descriptions["23761"]={cn:"为任何有自尊的滋滋量身定做！",en:"A luxury belt for any self-respecting boo!"};
descriptions["23762"]={cn:"轻易黏住狡猾的敌人。",en:"This shield is ideal for taking care of those slippery opponents."};
descriptions["23763"]={cn:"轻易黏住狡猾的敌人。",en:"This shield is ideal for taking care of those slippery opponents."};
descriptions["23764"]={cn:"洗完脸后带上，能让皮肤细腻红润有光泽。",en:"If you put the mask on right after cleansing, it will make you skin soft and radiant."};
descriptions["23765"]={cn:"总有苍蝇围着你飞。它们本来是围着便便飞的，吃饭的时候别说这么恶心的事...",en:"These epaulettes will have the flies in your vicinity dropping like, well, flies."};
descriptions["23766"]={cn:"由干燥的糊糊便便制成。不推荐用作求婚戒指。",en:"This ring was sculpted from dried Mushd droppings. We don\'t recommend you use it for marriage proposals."};
descriptions["23767"]={cn:"好吧，你知道吗？沙皇触角终于派上用处了！",en:"Well, whaddya know? The TsarTsar Horn finally has a use!"};
descriptions["23768"]={cn:"只需轻轻一咬，就能撕碎你的牙齿：女士们，早就提醒过你们不要接近大灰狼了！",en:"This delicate breastplate can tear your teeth apart with one single bite: ladies, you have been warned what will happen if you get too close to the big bad Boowolf."};
descriptions["23769"]={cn:"可以窃取魔族灵魂碎片的法杖。不过，这只是一件便宜的赝品。",en:"The Tumboler Staff was a weapon capable of stealing pieces of Shushu souls. Unfortunately, this Tumboler Staff is just a cheap replica."};
descriptions["23770"]={cn:"当心，睡着的时候它也会盯着你。",en:"Beware of this amulet. It will watch you when you sleep."};
descriptions["23771"]={cn:"主要面向喜欢暴晒脚趾的人群。不用说，市场反应好极了。",en:"Mainly marketed towards those who love tanning their toes but not the rest of their feet. Needless to say, they sell like hotcakes."};
descriptions["23772"]={cn:"使你成为贤明的皇帝。",en:"This cloak will set you on your way to becoming the rightful tsar."};
descriptions["23773"]={cn:"亲爱的，它碎掉了。",en:"This ring is absolutely cracking, dahling."};
descriptions["23774"]={cn:"亲爱的，它碎掉了。",en:"This ring is absolutely cracking, dahling."};
descriptions["23775"]={cn:"来吧，穿着它踏碎地面！",en:"Go on, have a crack at walking in these!"};
descriptions["23776"]={cn:"来吧，穿着它踏碎地面！",en:"Go on, have a crack at walking in these!"};
descriptions["23777"]={cn:"看起来破破烂烂，但是能让你安然无恙。",en:"This helmet might look pretty beat-up but there\'s some life in it yet."};
descriptions["23778"]={cn:"看起来破破烂烂，但是能让你安然无恙。",en:"This helmet might look pretty beat-up but there\'s some life in it yet."};
descriptions["23779"]={cn:"不要在肩甲的重压下崩溃。",en:"Make sure you don\'t crack under the strain of these epaulettes."};
descriptions["23780"]={cn:"并不太锋利，但是依然能给人以疼痛。",en:"This blade may not be sharp, but it certainly smarts!"};
descriptions["23781"]={cn:"并不太锋利，但是依然能给人以疼痛。",en:"This blade may not be sharp, but it certainly smarts!"};
descriptions["23782"]={cn:"只要你能拿起来，就能狠狠打痛敌人。",en:"This hammer hits hard, if you can pick it up."};
descriptions["23783"]={cn:"你忍不住想打自己的头，也包括敌人的头！",en:"The only breastplate that will make you want to bop your head - and your enemies\' heads!"};
descriptions["23784"]={cn:"据说能为佩戴者带来神秘的强作微笑的力量。仔细看看，你就知道这股力量一点也不神秘了。",en:"This ring is said to confer a mystical smile-cracking power on its wearer. Looking at it, though, perhaps it\'s not so mystical after all."};
descriptions["23785"]={cn:"自从绵球球大赛禁止穿寒石靴以后，到处都可以买到它们。显然不是什么高级货。",en:"These boots have been readily available ever since they were banned from Gobbowl tournaments. Apparently they weren\'t hardcore enough."};
descriptions["23786"]={cn:"不是个拿来跑100卡米的好选择。在千洞林藏身还不错。",en:"A bad cloak for running the 100 kameters in. A good cloak for blending into your surroundings in the Holey Forest!"};
descriptions["23787"]={cn:"见过碎石者表演一种古代摔跤技巧...头槌吗？你见到的时候，最好戴着这顶头盔。",en:"If you\'ve ever seen a Crackrock performing the ancient fight move known as a headbutt, you\'ll know that you\'re better off inside this helmet than out."};
descriptions["23788"]={cn:"看来有人经常写错别字...没有人会当着你的面提起这件事，尤其是当你脸色铁青的时候。",en:"Looks like someone came last in the spelling bee... All the same, nobody would ever say it to your face, not when you look this scary."};
descriptions["23789"]={cn:"别担心，还能穿很多年。",en:"Don\'t worry, it\'ll last for years yet."};
descriptions["23790"]={cn:"用于挖掘大石块，挖小碎石也很有效。",en:"Great for digging up large stones and little Crackrocks."};
descriptions["23791"]={cn:"两个脑袋总好过一个...前提是脑袋里还有东西。",en:"Two craniums are better than one... As long as they\'ve got something in them."};
descriptions["23792"]={cn:"两个脑袋总好过一个...前提是脑袋里还有东西。",en:"Two craniums are better than one... As long as they\'ve got something in them."};
descriptions["23793"]={cn:"如果你想留住这条项链，不要把它塞在枕头下面！",en:"If you want to hold on to this necklace, don\'t put it under your pillow."};
descriptions["23794"]={cn:"如果你想留住这条项链，不要把它塞在枕头下面！",en:"If you want to hold on to this necklace, don\'t put it under your pillow."};
descriptions["23795"]={cn:"你知道让别人不再把你叫做没骨头的胆小鬼的最好方法吗？",en:"Who knew it would be so easy to stop people from calling you a spineless coward?"};
descriptions["23796"]={cn:"你知道让别人不再把你叫做没骨头的胆小鬼的最好方法吗？",en:"Who knew it would be so easy to stop people from calling you a spineless coward?"};
descriptions["23797"]={cn:"既能用作凉鞋也能用作靴子。在雨天里无法保证你的袜子干爽。穿起来还算舒适。",en:"Half sandal, half boot, these won\'t keep your socks dry in the rain. Serves you right for wearing them."};
descriptions["23798"]={cn:"如果你讨厌骨头咯吱咯吱的声音，那千万不要选择这把弓。",en:"If you hate the sound of bones cracking, this definitely isn\'t the weapon for you."};
descriptions["23799"]={cn:"如果你讨厌骨头咯吱咯吱的声音，那千万不要选择这把弓。",en:"If you hate the sound of bones cracking, this definitely isn\'t the weapon for you."};
descriptions["23800"]={cn:"狂战士选择穿骸骨凉鞋来刺激自己。因为它们穿起来实在太痛了。",en:"Sacriers often wear these sandals to stimulate themselves. Because they\'re so painful to wear, of course."};
descriptions["23801"]={cn:"考虑到年岁久远，盾牌已经很脆弱了。它不再能抵挡攻击。主要卖点是看上去很吓人。",en:"It\'s not surprising this shield is very fragile given its age. It doesn\'t offer much in the way of protection any more, either. Its main selling point is the hostile aspect of its appearance."};
descriptions["23802"]={cn:"曾经属于屠夫梅茨格，他切骨头的时候用的就是这把刀。一个骸骨士兵从他那里偷到了这把刀。从那以后，刀下断肢者层出不穷。",en:"This Blade once belonged to Metzger the Butcher, who used it to cut up bones. A Chafer managed to steal it from him and, in his hands, the blade has been responsible for numerous amputations."};
descriptions["23803"]={cn:"依附着骸骨之王的灵魂。睡觉的时候别戴着，否则鼻子会莫名抽搐。",en:"This amulet was bewitched by the spirit of the Chafer King. Unless you want it to make your nose twitch uncontrollably, it\'s best not to wear it in bed."};
descriptions["23804"]={cn:"骸骨之王只在特殊场合才穿上这件披风。事实上，他是穿着这件披风被干掉的。",en:"The Chafer King only wears this cloak for special occasions. As a matter of fact, it just so happened that he was wearing it the day he was killed."};
descriptions["23805"]={cn:"这对护肩的起源是一个黑暗、深邃的秘密。我们只知道它们有着强大的力量。",en:"The origin of these epaulettes is a dark, deep secret. All that is known is that they have great powers."};
descriptions["23806"]={cn:"让人联想到一位著名的刺客。",en:"This amulet is somehow reminiscent of a certain, well-known Sram."};
descriptions["23807"]={cn:"这件披风并不能成为你游手好闲、到处乱逛，把自己装成白骨精的理由。",en:"This is not an excuse to spend the day stalking around pretending to be the king from Game of Bones."};
descriptions["23808"]={cn:"带着它，保证你不会再变胖了。",en:"At least with this belt, you can be sure you\'ll never get fat."};
descriptions["23809"]={cn:"拿两张骨牌相互剐蹭，发出的刺耳响声足以恶心死骸骨之王。",en:"Scraping these cards against one another creates a high, grinding sound, piercing enough to wake a Chafer."};
descriptions["23810"]={cn:"坚硬的白骨胸甲，能防止小矮人攻击你的头。",en:"A tough little breastplate that will put an end to short people trying to headbutt you."};
descriptions["23811"]={cn:"很明显，这只戒指曾经和噬影之牙是一对。不幸的是，他们最终分手了，因为彼此天各一方。异地恋必须死。",en:"Apparently, this ring once had a bit of a fling with Shadofang. Unfortunately, they broke up because Ringmote was a bit distant."};
descriptions["23812"]={cn:"很明显，这只戒指曾经和噬影之牙是一对。不幸的是，他们最终分手了，因为彼此天各一方。异地恋必须死。",en:"Apparently, this ring once had a bit of a fling with Shadofang. Unfortunately, they broke up because Ringmote was a bit distant."};
descriptions["23813"]={cn:"不要把这件披风留在你的庇护袋里，否则你会发现里面长出石笋来。当你后背感到刺痛的时候，你只能怪你自己了...",en:"Don\'t leave this cape in the bottom of your Haven Bag or you could find stalagmites growing in it. You\'ll only have yourself to blame when your back starts hurting..."};
descriptions["23814"]={cn:"不要把这件披风留在你的庇护袋里，否则你会发现里面长出石笋来。当你后背感到刺痛的时候，你只能怪你自己了...",en:"Don\'t leave this cape in the bottom of your Haven Bag or you could find stalagmites growing in it. You\'ll only have yourself to blame when your back starts hurting..."};
descriptions["23815"]={cn:"梦想着坚如磐石？现在你做得到了。",en:"Want to be a solid as a rock?  Now you can."};
descriptions["23816"]={cn:"梦想着坚如磐石？现在你做得到了。",en:"Want to be a solid as a rock?  Now you can."};
descriptions["23817"]={cn:"这条原装的腰带轻若无物。一不小心你会发现它卡住了。",en:"This original belt won\'t stand for any weight gain when you\'re wearing it. If you\'re not careful, you might find yourself stuck in it..."};
descriptions["23818"]={cn:"热血勇士都爱这顶头盔！如果你决定戴上它，就准备迎接火星四射的战斗吧。",en:"Hot-blooded warriors will love this helmet! If you decide to wear it, though, be prepared for hot flashes."};
descriptions["23819"]={cn:"热血勇士都爱这顶头盔！如果你决定戴上它，就准备迎接火星四射的战斗吧。",en:"Hot-blooded warriors will love this helmet! If you decide to wear it, though, be prepared for hot flashes."};
descriptions["23820"]={cn:"传说中的圣剑！如果你有能力将它从石头中拔出，你将成为真正的统治者。",en:"This sword is the stuff of legends! You can use it to show your enemies who really rules the roost, if you can get it out of the stone."};
descriptions["23821"]={cn:"没有老母护肩那么珍贵，但也不失为一件好装备。",en:"While less flamboyant than Mamagmulettes, the Stalagettes are a must for rock n\' roll parties."};
descriptions["23822"]={cn:"石头一样沉重！",en:"Aside from their unquestionable utility as boots, they can also be used in a pinch as a bludgeon."};
descriptions["23823"]={cn:"石笋老母的那一层岩浆让你的脚永远保持温暖，即便在大热天！",en:"Carved directly out of the Mamagmote\'s magmatic breastplate, these Mamagboots will keep you warm all winter! And all summer too!"};
descriptions["23824"]={cn:"虽然说是老母头盔，实际上是石笋宝宝出生的时候那些顶破的蛋壳做的。那么蛋是从哪里来的呢？",en:"Although its name may lead you to believe it\'s a helmet, it\'s actually the skull of a stalagmote fetus from an egg ripped from the Mamagmote\'s abdomen."};
descriptions["23825"]={cn:"原本脆弱的笋变得像石头一样坚硬，从里到外的坚硬。",en:"Even the Mamagmote\'s internal organs are protected by a rocky exoskeleton, like this heart valve."};
descriptions["23826"]={cn:"因为石笋老母而膨胀起来的石笋。",en:"A good beating stick made out of a Mamagmote pumped with hormones."};
descriptions["23827"]={cn:"既然你可以用这个护符诅咒敌人，为什么还要拚命地在战场上奔波呢？",en:"Why waste your time glowering across the battlefield at your enemy when you can just curse them using this amulet?"};
descriptions["23828"]={cn:"洪水激发了这柄剑的潜能。它从水中吸取了新的复仇力量。",en:"The flood seems to have been hugely beneficial to this blessed sword, which has drawn a new and vengeful power from the water."};
descriptions["23829"]={cn:"As in wood from a Birch tree, not a rod used for punishment. Then again, why not?...",en:"As in wood from a Birch tree, not a rod used for punishment. Then again, why not?..."};
descriptions["23830"]={cn:"This Cawwot is magical: it attracts all of the Wabbits in the area.",en:"This Cawwot is magical: it attracts all of the Wabbits in the area."};
descriptions["23831"]={cn:"Contrary to what its name may imply, this doesn\'t actually come from Chillberg Island.",en:"Contrary to what its name may imply, this doesn\'t actually come from Chillberg Island."};
descriptions["23832"]={cn:"Although it is extremely rare, you have difficulty understanding why.",en:"Although it is extremely rare, you have difficulty understanding why."};
descriptions["23833"]={cn:"Its finesse could even sweeten a Taur.",en:"Its finesse could even sweeten a Taur."};
descriptions["23834"]={cn:"This cobalt thinks no one can understand it. Just like other cobalts.",en:"This cobalt thinks no one can understand it. Just like other cobalts."};
descriptions["23835"]={cn:"You only came third. That allows you a place on the podium, but public renown is still quite far off...",en:"You only came third. That allows you a place on the podium, but public renown is still quite far off..."};
descriptions["23836"]={cn:"This is the subtle blend of the ocean\'s proteins and the medicinal properties of Hazelnutella.",en:"This is the subtle blend of the ocean\'s proteins and the medicinal properties of Hazelnutella."};
descriptions["23837"]={cn:"You could stare at this Loote for hours and still not find anything interesting about it.",en:"You could stare at this Loote for hours and still not find anything interesting about it."};
descriptions["23838"]={cn:"烫得难以拿捏！快点在它烧穿你的口袋，烫伤你的皮肤之前用掉！",en:"It\'s almost too hot to handle! Quick, spend it before it burns a hole in your pocket and then your epidermis!"};
descriptions["23839"]={cn:"历尽艰险的你赢得的奖励。你可以用这枚奖章兑换装备。",en:"You can trade in this hard-won token for pieces of equipment."};
descriptions["23840"]={cn:"历尽艰险的你赢得的奖励。你可以用这枚奖章兑换装备。",en:"You can trade in this hard-won token for pieces of equipment."};
descriptions["23841"]={cn:"历尽艰险的你赢得的奖励。你可以用这枚奖章兑换装备。",en:"You can trade in this hard-won token for pieces of equipment."};
descriptions["23842"]={cn:"历尽艰险的你赢得的奖励。你可以用这枚奖章兑换装备。",en:"You can trade in this hard-won token for pieces of equipment."};
descriptions["23843"]={cn:"用于在南瓜节化妆舞会上扮成狂狼...记得在亲吻心上人的时候拿下来！",en:"These fangs are just what you need to complete your Moowolf Al Howin\'s outfit... Just remember to take them off if you\'re kissing your sweetheart."};
descriptions["23844"]={cn:"穿上这个胸甲，上看下看左看右看，怎么看你都像...像头野兽。",en:"With one of these ferocious specimens on your front and one on your back, you\'ll look like... well, a beast with two backs."};
descriptions["23845"]={cn:"散发着一股充满野性的气味，让你忍不住想冲着满月嚎叫。",en:"This cloak has a beastly smell that risks causing undesirable secondary effects that will send you howling to the moon."};
descriptions["23846"]={cn:"穿上它，可以让你涉足那些无法到达的地方。注意，在家里或者办公室的地板上就不要穿了。",en:"An accessory made for scratching hard-to-get-to places - just what you needed! A word of advice, though: with claws like that, you shouldn\'t use it anywhere... sensitive."};
descriptions["23847"]={cn:"每走一小步，腰带上的小铃铛都会剧烈摇动，任何人都会察觉到你在偷偷接近。漂亮和惊喜二选一。",en:"The little bells that adorn this belt jingle so violently that they make it impossible to sneak up on anyone. Look, it was either style or surprise. You can\'t have both!"};
descriptions["23848"]={cn:"只需一击就可以让巨魔昏迷不醒。问题是，你拿得起来吗？",en:"One blow of this club is enough to decapitate a Trool. The question is, are you strong enough to pick it up?"};
descriptions["23850"]={cn:"狼牙深深嵌入你的手指！",en:"It\'ll sink its fangs into your finger!"};
descriptions["23851"]={cn:"现在你可以戴着铃铛攻击敌人了！",en:"Now you can attack your enemies with bells on!"};
descriptions["23852"]={cn:"傲然立于狼群之首！",en:"Stand tall and proud in this headgear!"};
descriptions["23853"]={cn:"用于联结喀努斯的灵魂和神圣绵球的躯壳。属于灵体的强大法器...你能够驾驭这股强大的力量吗？",en:"This piece of jewelry was used to link Excarnus\'s soul to Gobbsage\'s ethereal body. A powerful artifact in the hands of an Excarnate... Do you really think you\'re capable of using its power?"};
descriptions["23854"]={cn:"作为气嘘者友好的主人曾经指出，这个靴子会给你带来各种各样的气势。",en:"As Gasper the friendly host once pointed out, these boots give you all sorts of airs and graces."};
descriptions["23855"]={cn:"很不错的狩猎战利品！",en:"A well-earned hunting trophy!"};
descriptions["23856"]={cn:"这件蕴含强大力量的胸甲被一股无名的气息所包裹，卷卷的，有点娘。",en:"This breastplate\'s curly virility is counteracted by the ectoplasmic gloop all over it. Talk about ruining the mood."};
descriptions["23857"]={cn:"这段薄纱能让覆盖着的恶灵隐身。很多人为了找到这件稀世珍宝而付出了本来就不怎么正常的理智。",en:"A transparent veil which enables excarnates to become invisible. Many a man is pushing up daisies after trying too hard to obtain this precious item."};
descriptions["23858"]={cn:"挖掘一切零零碎碎。",en:"This shovel is useful for unearthing all kinds of bits and pieces."};
descriptions["23859"]={cn:"是的，它打人很痛！",en:"And yes, it really hurts!"};
descriptions["23860"]={cn:"厚实的披风，让你温暖备至！",en:"This incredibly thick coat will keep you... incredibly warm!"};
descriptions["23861"]={cn:"如果你看到有人穿着这对护肩攻击你，看在幸运猫的份上，马上转身逃跑吧！",en:"If you see someone charging towards you wearing these epaulettes, then for Eca\'s sake run as fast as you can in the other direction!"};
descriptions["23862"]={cn:"造型独特的头盔，让其他冒险者像绵绵一样在你周围聚集。",en:"This impressively-built helmet will cause adventurers to come flocking around you like Gobblies. Oh, wait..."};
descriptions["23863"]={cn:"纪念你与神圣绵球的战斗。",en:"This amulet is a fine souvenir of your battle with Gobbsage."};
descriptions["23864"]={cn:"不要被柔软的绒毛欺骗了，这件胸甲切大石如切黄油。而且并不能保证使用者的人身安全。",en:"Don\'t be fooled by the softness of the wool, this breastplate will cut rocks like butter. It doesn\'t guarantee the safety of its wearer, however."};
descriptions["23865"]={cn:"锻炼身体，铲除地下怪兽，造型别致，谁用谁知道。",en:"It moves us with its underground beats and gets us our exercise. Given its irregular curves, it\'s only beneficial for the one carrying it."};
descriptions["23866"]={cn:"僵尸铲上都是刺，想要运用自如就得戴上这种手套。",en:"The Zombo is covered with splinters, so it\'s necessary to wear these gloves if you want to dance with it successfully."};
descriptions["23867"]={cn:"Arachnee Silk is so sticky that you can use it to repair any broken item. You\'ll just have to unstick it from your fingers first...",en:"Arachnee Silk is so sticky that you can use it to repair any broken item. You\'ll just have to unstick it from your fingers first..."};
descriptions["23868"]={cn:"It stinks, it\'s rotten, and it\'s disgusting, but at least it\'s useful.",en:"It stinks, it\'s rotten, and it\'s disgusting, but at least it\'s useful."};
descriptions["23869"]={cn:"The spinal column makes a pleasant sound when you shake it. Even better, Bow Wows and Bow Meows love to chew on it!",en:"The spinal column makes a pleasant sound when you shake it. Even better, Bow Wows and Bow Meows love to chew on it!"};
descriptions["23870"]={cn:"当心！如果一不小心溅在衣服上就永远洗不干净了！",en:"Careful: If you drop some on your clothes, you\'ll never get the stain out!"};
descriptions["23872"]={cn:"Welcome to Ember Island, where we\'re burning up the dance floor! Grab a guy or girly and get whirly, bang out a rhythm on your koko-drums, and let\'s samba, mis amigos!",en:"Welcome to Ember Island, where we\'re burning up the dance floor! Grab a guy or girly and get whirly, bang out a rhythm on your koko-drums, and let\'s samba, mis amigos!"};
descriptions["23873"]={cn:"Plunge into the depths of time and feel the power of the god Xelor for a just an moment... AN EVERLASTING MOMENT!",en:"Plunge into the depths of time and feel the power of the god Xelor for a just an moment... AN EVERLASTING MOMENT!"};
descriptions["23874"]={cn:"Royal is the aroma of warm sap that seeps from the Natroyal Costume. If you wear it in the middle of the the Treechnid Forest, you\'ll surely attract all of the Bow Wows taking a stroll!",en:"Royal is the aroma of warm sap that seeps from the Natroyal Costume. If you wear it in the middle of the the Treechnid Forest, you\'ll surely attract all of the Bow Wows taking a stroll!"};
descriptions["23876"]={cn:"Dressed up in this and with your voice sharpened, you\'ll finally be ready to fiercely battle it out to win the great summer kamaoke contest. And this end is justified by all the means you\'ll use.",en:"Dressed up in this and with your voice sharpened, you\'ll finally be ready to fiercely battle it out to win the great summer kamaoke contest. And this end is justified by all the means you\'ll use."};
descriptions["23877"]={cn:"When Riktus are sowing terror in a village, you put on your hero set for the night. If an asteroid is threatening World of Twelve, you slip into your super-avenger costume. But make no mistake: Stopping a war is a job for the Wonder Costume.",en:"When Riktus are sowing terror in a village, you put on your hero set for the night. If an asteroid is threatening World of Twelve, you slip into your super-avenger costume. But make no mistake: Stopping a war is a job for the Wonder Costume."};
descriptions["23878"]={cn:"Only the god Osamodas knows what you\'ve been feeding your <b>Dragominus</b> or your <b>Gradon</b>, but there\'s no denying it\'s developed a powerful thirst for blood!",en:"Only the god Osamodas knows what you\'ve been feeding your <b>Dragominus</b> or your <b>Gradon</b>, but there\'s no denying it\'s developed a powerful thirst for blood!"};
descriptions["23879"]={cn:"此庇护袋外观为你完成一个十二世界挑战后的奖励！",en:"This Haven Bag Kit is your reward for completing a World of Twelve challenge!"};
descriptions["23880"]={cn:"此庇护袋外观为你完成一个十二世界挑战后的奖励！",en:"This Haven Bag Kit is your reward for completing a World of Twelve challenge!"};
descriptions["23881"]={cn:"What could this strange mechanical creature be? In any case, it seems to be attracted to anything living. So cute!!!",en:"What could this strange mechanical creature be? In any case, it seems to be attracted to anything living. So cute!!!"};
descriptions["23883"]={cn:"使用后会启动或关闭终结技。此物品不可堆叠。发动时会从启动的终结技里随机发动一个。",en:"Using this will activate or deactivate the Finisher. The item is not consumed. Random selection among all active Finishers."};
descriptions["23884"]={cn:"使用时可以让你切换跑步的方式，这个物品不会被消耗。",en:"When used, this item activates or deactivates the change of running. The item is not consumed."};
descriptions["23885"]={cn:"由泽尼特佣兵重新装订而成，非常珍贵的百科全书。",en:"The incredibly valuable reassembled encyclopedia of the Mount Zinit Mercenaries."};
descriptions["23886"]={cn:"Measured, like the choices you\'ve made in evolving your Tofu. It looks like you\'ve succeeded brilliantly!",en:"Measured, like the choices you\'ve made in evolving your Tofu. It looks like you\'ve succeeded brilliantly!"};
descriptions["23887"]={cn:"Don\'t look now, but you may have been overfeeding your Tofu a bit...",en:"Don\'t look now, but you may have been overfeeding your Tofu a bit..."};
descriptions["23888"]={cn:"Your Tofu was doomed to lifelong ickiness... once you became its owner!",en:"Your Tofu was doomed to lifelong ickiness... once you became its owner!"};
descriptions["23889"]={cn:"This is one truly fine Tofu.",en:"This is one truly fine Tofu."};
descriptions["23890"]={cn:"你的豆芙就像个歌手，不是会唱歌的那种，但一样迷人！",en:"Your Tofu is a diva, and not the kind that sings, but a star just the same!"};
descriptions["23891"]={cn:"Aggressive and irritable, your Tofu must have been seriously deprived of love when it was young.",en:"Aggressive and irritable, your Tofu must have been seriously deprived of love when it was young."};
descriptions["23892"]={cn:"Your Bow Meow has developed in a perfectly normal manner thanks to your disciplined supervision.",en:"Your Bow Meow has developed in a perfectly normal manner thanks to your disciplined supervision."};
descriptions["23893"]={cn:"A Bow Meow this huge will be the butt of a thousand jokes. When this thing sits around the house... it really sits AROUND the house.",en:"A Bow Meow this huge will be the butt of a thousand jokes. When this thing sits around the house... it really sits AROUND the house."};
descriptions["23894"]={cn:"Your lack of attention to your Bow Meow\'s hygiene borders on criminal neglect. Shame on you.",en:"Your lack of attention to your Bow Meow\'s hygiene borders on criminal neglect. Shame on you."};
descriptions["23895"]={cn:"Your Bow Meow is obedient and kind, thanks to the training you\'ve given it.",en:"Your Bow Meow is obedient and kind, thanks to the training you\'ve given it."};
descriptions["23896"]={cn:"Your Charming Bow Meow bows and meows most bewitchingly, making Bow Meowettes\' hearts melt and lashes bat twitchingly.",en:"Your Charming Bow Meow bows and meows most bewitchingly, making Bow Meowettes\' hearts melt and lashes bat twitchingly."};
descriptions["23897"]={cn:"这是一只非常难以接近的喵喵，真讨人厌！",en:"This is one seriously unapproachable Bow Meow. What a nasty piece of work!"};
descriptions["23898"]={cn:"You\'ve shown great skill in guiding your Boon\'s evolution.",en:"You\'ve shown great skill in guiding your Boon\'s evolution."};
descriptions["23899"]={cn:"Safe to say that your Boon has never had to go hungry.",en:"Safe to say that your Boon has never had to go hungry."};
descriptions["23900"]={cn:"It\'s not your fault if your Boon is allergic to cleanliness!",en:"It\'s not your fault if your Boon is allergic to cleanliness!"};
descriptions["23901"]={cn:"Your Boon is always happy to see you, but don\'t leave it alone for a second.",en:"Your Boon is always happy to see you, but don\'t leave it alone for a second."};
descriptions["23902"]={cn:"Who would have thought that a Boon could be so cute?",en:"Who would have thought that a Boon could be so cute?"};
descriptions["23903"]={cn:"暴躁又独立的笨丁。你觉得自己正看着个杜尔德。",en:"What a whiny but independent Boon. You\'d swear you were looking at a Deuldeu."};
descriptions["23922"]={cn:"能够放在庇护袋中，将不需要的物品转化为符文粉末，用于制作新物品！",en:"To be placed in your Haven Bag, the Item Recycler will allow you to crush any item you no longer need in order to make powders, which can then be used to make new items!"};
descriptions["23924"]={cn:"这条护符曾经属於一位掌握了四种原初元素能量的光能法师，但显然造化（或奥古）弄人啊。",en:"This amulet once belonged to a Huppermage who mastered the four primordial elemental energies. Apparently, fate (or Ogrest) played a trick on him."};
descriptions["23925"]={cn:"啸风项链在周围风和蒸汽的带动下能产生可观的能量。据说其旋转的力量极强，要是有好奇的布丁靠太近，有可能会被吹散到十二世界的四角。",en:"The Amulet of Howlieng Wind produces impressive energy in the presence of ambient winds and vapors. It is said that the power of its rotation is so strong that a curious Puddly could end up being scattered to the four corners of the World of Twelve if it came too close."};
descriptions["23926"]={cn:"使用物品栏上方的分解按钮将这件物品回收为附魔碎片。",en:"This item must be converted into shards using the Recycle button at the top of the inventory window."};
descriptions["23927"]={cn:"使用物品栏上方的分解按钮将这件物品回收为附魔碎片。",en:"This item must be converted into shards using the Recycle button at the top of the inventory window."};
descriptions["23928"]={cn:"使用物品栏上方的分解按钮将这件物品回收为附魔碎片。",en:"This item must be converted into shards using the Recycle button at the top of the inventory window."};
descriptions["23940"]={cn:"Life could be a lot nicer out in the desert.",en:"Life could be a lot nicer out in the desert."};
descriptions["23941"]={cn:"What made you decide to collect the gooey stuff left behind by the Blackspores? It\'s because it was shiny, huh?",en:"What made you decide to collect the gooey stuff left behind by the Blackspores? It\'s because it was shiny, huh?"};
descriptions["23942"]={cn:"穿上这件服装，你会感受到一层深层的连结，连结着森林以及循环于所有生命间的能量网，",en:"By wearing this costume, you\'ll feel a deep connection with the forest and the network of energy circulating in all living things."};
descriptions["23943"]={cn:"这只小福狸好可爱，不想抱一个吗？好痛！小心手指！",en:"Oh, he\'s so cute, this Li\'l Lenald, don\'t you just want to cuddle him? OUCH! Watch the fingers!"};
descriptions["23944"]={cn:"狂欢节是一年中唯一的一天，没人把自己隐藏在面具之下的日子。",en:"Karnaval day is the only day of the year when no one hides themself by wearing a mask."};
descriptions["23945"]={cn:"穿上后取决于你角色的性别，会看起来像是最富有活力的啦啦队员，或硬派的体育播报员。",en:"Depending on the gender of your character, putting on this costume will either make you look like the most energetic cheerleader ever, or a hardened sports commentator."};
descriptions["23946"]={cn:"你能成功收集所有部分吗？",en:"Will you succeed in collecting all the pieces?"};
descriptions["23947"]={cn:"你能成功收集所有部分吗？",en:"Will you succeed in collecting all the pieces?"};
descriptions["23948"]={cn:"你能成功收集所有部分吗？",en:"Will you succeed in collecting all the pieces?"};
