descriptions["23950"]={cn:"你能成功收集所有部分吗？",en:"Will you succeed in collecting all the pieces?"};
descriptions["23951"]={cn:"现在你能对朋友嚎哭得像奥古一样，肯定能让他们开眼界。但别对你另一半这样做，不会有你预期的效果。",en:"Now you\'ll be able to wail like Ogrest to your friends, which will impress them for sure. But avoid doing so to your other half, because it won\'t have the desired effect."};
descriptions["23952"]={cn:"你能成功收集所有部分吗？",en:"Will you succeed in collecting all the pieces?"};
