descriptions["23956"]={cn:"Have you always dreamed of being able to dance with your friends like one of those famous cheerleaders? Now you can!",en:"Have you always dreamed of being able to dance with your friends like one of those famous cheerleaders? Now you can!"};
descriptions["23957"]={cn:"此庇护袋外观为你完成一个十二世界挑战后的奖励！",en:"This Haven Bag Kit is your reward for completing a World of Twelve challenge!"};
descriptions["23958"]={cn:"This Young Drheller is such a joker that it will never stop looking for treasure for its master.",en:"This Young Drheller is such a joker that it will never stop looking for treasure for its master."};
descriptions["23959"]={cn:"When your enemies see these boots, they\'ll feel like rats on a sinking ship.",en:"When your enemies see these boots, they\'ll feel like rats on a sinking ship."};
descriptions["23960"]={cn:"Ogrest\'s Tears are definitely at their most beautiful in a garden or a courtyard.",en:"Ogrest\'s Tears are definitely at their most beautiful in a garden or a courtyard."};
descriptions["23961"]={cn:"A priceless book.",en:"A priceless book."};
descriptions["23962"]={cn:"A small miniature that represents everything you went through to reach the Mount Zinit Summit. That was really tough... Especially on the way back down!",en:"A small miniature that represents everything you went through to reach the Mount Zinit Summit. That was really tough... Especially on the way back down!"};
descriptions["23963"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。\n打开它只需要两秒!",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with the mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["23964"]={cn:"收集 100 块碎片，合成鼠王礼靴。",en:"Collect 100 of these fragments to create a pair of Lord of the Rats\' Ceremonial Boots."};
descriptions["23965"]={cn:"These scorching-hot claws recall the blazing infernos created by their owner. Ignemikhal can be violent at times, and his fury now takes hold of you.",en:"These scorching-hot claws recall the blazing infernos created by their owner. Ignemikhal can be violent at times, and his fury now takes hold of you."};
descriptions["23966"]={cn:"These scorching-hot claws recall the blazing infernos created by their owner. Ignemikhal can be violent at times, and his fury now takes hold of you.",en:"These scorching-hot claws recall the blazing infernos created by their owner. Ignemikhal can be violent at times, and his fury now takes hold of you."};
descriptions["23967"]={cn:"The original wearer of these scales was once charmed by Dathura. You\'ll experience the owner\'s calm even as you imagine the raging tempests he can unleash.",en:"The original wearer of these scales was once charmed by Dathura. You\'ll experience the owner\'s calm even as you imagine the raging tempests he can unleash."};
descriptions["23968"]={cn:"The original wearer of these scales was once charmed by Dathura. You\'ll experience the owner\'s calm even as you imagine the raging tempests he can unleash.",en:"The original wearer of these scales was once charmed by Dathura. You\'ll experience the owner\'s calm even as you imagine the raging tempests he can unleash."};
descriptions["23969"]={cn:"Dardondakal loves to play in the space between wisdom and jest. You now have one of its claws - all you\'re missing is its whiskers.",en:"Dardondakal loves to play in the space between wisdom and jest. You now have one of its claws - all you\'re missing is its whiskers."};
descriptions["23970"]={cn:"Dardondakal loves to play in the space between wisdom and jest. You now have one of its claws - all you\'re missing is its whiskers.",en:"Dardondakal loves to play in the space between wisdom and jest. You now have one of its claws - all you\'re missing is its whiskers."};
descriptions["23971"]={cn:"A bittersweet melancholy takes hold of you when you put on these boots. Terrakourial seems to have lived a long life, filled with regrets that can still be felt.",en:"A bittersweet melancholy takes hold of you when you put on these boots. Terrakourial seems to have lived a long life, filled with regrets that can still be felt."};
descriptions["23972"]={cn:"A bittersweet melancholy takes hold of you when you put on these boots. Terrakourial seems to have lived a long life, filled with regrets that can still be felt.",en:"A bittersweet melancholy takes hold of you when you put on these boots. Terrakourial seems to have lived a long life, filled with regrets that can still be felt."};
descriptions["23973"]={cn:"These graceful wings embody the dignity of Aerafal, master of the skies. Those who wear them project a haughty air.",en:"These graceful wings embody the dignity of Aerafal, master of the skies. Those who wear them project a haughty air."};
descriptions["23974"]={cn:"These graceful wings embody the dignity of Aerafal, master of the skies. Those who wear them project a haughty air.",en:"These graceful wings embody the dignity of Aerafal, master of the skies. Those who wear them project a haughty air."};
descriptions["23975"]={cn:"A strange torment seems to emanate from this helmet. Grougalorasalar is a dragon that is as impulsive as it is complex. None can predict what this skull will do for you.",en:"A strange torment seems to emanate from this helmet. Grougalorasalar is a dragon that is as impulsive as it is complex. None can predict what this skull will do for you."};
descriptions["23976"]={cn:"A strange torment seems to emanate from this helmet. Grougalorasalar is a dragon that is as impulsive as it is complex. None can predict what this skull will do for you.",en:"A strange torment seems to emanate from this helmet. Grougalorasalar is a dragon that is as impulsive as it is complex. None can predict what this skull will do for you."};
descriptions["23977"]={cn:"许多人会一头倒在这副肩甲上...痛哭。奥古的手下败将多不胜数，而会流泪的可不只他而已。",en:"Many men will rest their heads on these epaulettes... to cry. There have been many defeats at the hands of Ogrest, and the Ogre certainly has no monopoly on tears."};
descriptions["23978"]={cn:"许多人会一头倒在这副肩甲上...痛哭。奥古的手下败将多不胜数，而会流泪的可不只他而已。",en:"Many men will rest their heads on these epaulettes... to cry. There have been many defeats at the hands of Ogrest, and the Ogre certainly has no monopoly on tears."};
descriptions["23979"]={cn:"某天，一位英雄只身对上了奥古。他来，他见，他打着赤膊落荒而逃。",en:"One day, a lonely hero sought to face Ogrest one-on-one. He came, he saw, he scampered away topless."};
descriptions["23980"]={cn:"某天，一位英雄只身对上了奥古。他来，他见，他打着赤膊落荒而逃。",en:"One day, a lonely hero sought to face Ogrest one-on-one. He came, he saw, he scampered away topless."};
descriptions["23981"]={cn:"一旦戴上，除了戴这戒指以外会遗忘其它用手的方法。最好还是戴在敌人手指上比较好。",en:"Once you put it on, forget about doing anything else with your hand. You\'ll be better off putting this ring on an enemy\'s finger."};
descriptions["23982"]={cn:"一旦戴上，除了戴这戒指以外会遗忘其它用手的方法。最好还是戴在敌人手指上比较好。",en:"Once you put it on, forget about doing anything else with your hand. You\'ll be better off putting this ring on an enemy\'s finger."};
descriptions["23983"]={cn:"这件物品属於古代的一位航海家，总是会指向穿戴者最渴望的事物。",en:"This artifact from an ancient navigator always points towards whatever the wearer desires most."};
descriptions["23984"]={cn:"这件物品属於古代的一位航海家，总是会指向穿戴者最渴望的事物。",en:"This artifact from an ancient navigator always points towards whatever the wearer desires most."};
descriptions["23985"]={cn:"事实上，这条护符不会给你带来好运，但戴起来的确会有某种功效。",en:"The truth is, this amulet won\'t bring you good luck. But it does have a certain effect when you place it around your neck."};
descriptions["23986"]={cn:"事实上，这条护符不会给你带来好运，但戴起来的确会有某种功效。",en:"The truth is, this amulet won\'t bring you good luck. But it does have a certain effect when you place it around your neck."};
descriptions["23987"]={cn:"要是这双靴子不会每踩一步就散发出一股味道的话，是有可能被遗忘。力量有其代价...和味道！",en:"These boots might be forgettable if it weren\'t for the odor they give off with every step you take. Power has its price... and quite a smell, too!"};
descriptions["23988"]={cn:"要是这双靴子不会每踩一步就散发出一股味道的话，是有可能被遗忘。力量有其代价...和味道！",en:"These boots might be forgettable if it weren\'t for the odor they give off with every step you take. Power has its price... and quite a smell, too!"};
descriptions["23989"]={cn:"要是他们搜寻你时只找得到你的腰带，很可能你戴着时也挺不好受的。",en:"If all they can find of you is your belt, chances are you\'ve had a pretty rough time of it."};
descriptions["23990"]={cn:"要是他们搜寻你时只找得到你的腰带，很可能你戴着时也挺不好受的。",en:"If all they can find of you is your belt, chances are you\'ve had a pretty rough time of it."};
descriptions["23991"]={cn:"这件披风是抵御了奥古的英勇战士唯一留下来的物品，依然能从其上看到那场艰险而短暂的战斗留下的痕迹。",en:"This cloak is all that remains of the valiant warrior who faced down Ogrest. It still bears the marks of a battle that was as terrible as it was brief."};
descriptions["23992"]={cn:"这件披风是抵御了奥古的英勇战士唯一留下来的物品，依然能从其上看到那场艰险而短暂的战斗留下的痕迹。",en:"This cloak is all that remains of the valiant warrior who faced down Ogrest. It still bears the marks of a battle that was as terrible as it was brief."};
descriptions["23993"]={cn:"许多冒险者尝试着对抗奥古，而随着那怪物手起拳落，他们留下了许多财宝。\n这顶头盔能在阿斯图布酒馆的地下室兑换成没有绑定的版本。",en:"Many an adventurer has tried to confront Ogrest, and they\'ve left many treasures behind after a few quick hits from the monster.\nThis helmet can be exchanged for an unlinked version in the basement of the Astrub Tavern."};
descriptions["23994"]={cn:"获取六颗原初龙蛋的渴望还能在你心里沈寂多久呢？",en:"How much longer will your thirst to gather the six Primordial Dofus remain unslaked?"};
descriptions["23995"]={cn:"获取六颗原初龙蛋的渴望还能在你心里沈寂多久呢？",en:"How much longer will your thirst to gather the six Primordial Dofus remain unslaked?"};
descriptions["23996"]={cn:"获取六颗原初龙蛋的渴望还能在你心里沈寂多久呢？",en:"How much longer will your thirst to gather the six Primordial Dofus remain unslaked?"};
