descriptions["23999"]={cn:"获取六颗原初龙蛋的渴望还能在你心里沈寂多久呢？",en:"How much longer will your thirst to gather the six Primordial Dofus remain unslaked?"};
descriptions["24000"]={cn:"With this sword in hand, you\'ll feel ready to bring peace and calm back to Mount Zinit.",en:"With this sword in hand, you\'ll feel ready to bring peace and calm back to Mount Zinit."};
descriptions["24001"]={cn:"Many fighters will bend the knee before the sword belonging to the lord of the brave. Some to be knighted... and others to beg for mercy.",en:"Many fighters will bend the knee before the sword belonging to the lord of the brave. Some to be knighted... and others to beg for mercy."};
descriptions["24002"]={cn:"This shovel turns up the most priceless of treasures, the key locks them away in the strongest of chests, and the weapon discourages even the wildest of thieves from approaching.",en:"This shovel turns up the most priceless of treasures, the key locks them away in the strongest of chests, and the weapon discourages even the wildest of thieves from approaching."};
descriptions["24003"]={cn:"This nasty little dagger always finds the quickest path to slip between your enemies\' ribs... or into your allies\' backs.",en:"This nasty little dagger always finds the quickest path to slip between your enemies\' ribs... or into your allies\' backs."};
descriptions["24004"]={cn:"Let governments fall, heroes stumble, justice fail and chaos rain down. Hope still lives on in one last line of defense: this shield.",en:"Let governments fall, heroes stumble, justice fail and chaos rain down. Hope still lives on in one last line of defense: this shield."};
descriptions["24005"]={cn:"When martyrs decide to become executioners, they take up this weapon to spill the blood of others.",en:"When martyrs decide to become executioners, they take up this weapon to spill the blood of others."};
descriptions["24006"]={cn:"This staff can bring forth an impressive burst of vegetation when it touches the ground, making the world a greener place with every step its bearer takes.",en:"This staff can bring forth an impressive burst of vegetation when it touches the ground, making the world a greener place with every step its bearer takes."};
descriptions["24007"]={cn:"Legend has it that this sacred weapon was used to create the Pandamurai, zealous defenders of the Bambooshido code.",en:"Legend has it that this sacred weapon was used to create the Pandamurai, zealous defenders of the Bambooshido code."};
descriptions["24008"]={cn:"When his whip was no longer sufficient to tame the most aggressive creatures, Osamodas decided to use a hammer instead.",en:"When his whip was no longer sufficient to tame the most aggressive creatures, Osamodas decided to use a hammer instead."};
descriptions["24009"]={cn:"This bow was made from Golden Apis, earning it great fame.\nIts bearer will be more than happy with its fearful aim.",en:"This bow was made from Golden Apis, earning it great fame.\nIts bearer will be more than happy with its fearful aim."};
descriptions["24010"]={cn:"Whether you need a straight, a pair, three or even four of a kind, these cards win every game and ensure you\'ve always got an ace in the hole.",en:"Whether you need a straight, a pair, three or even four of a kind, these cards win every game and ensure you\'ve always got an ace in the hole."};
descriptions["24011"]={cn:"Controlling the flow of time isn\'t always easy for the Great Clockmaker, as this hand will always be there to remind you.",en:"Controlling the flow of time isn\'t always easy for the Great Clockmaker, as this hand will always be there to remind you."};
