descriptions["24026"]={cn:"Once borne by the Goddess Eniripsa, but originally created by Eni Nooni.",en:"Once borne by the Goddess Eniripsa, but originally created by Eni Nooni."};
descriptions["24027"]={cn:"没有任何事物或任何人，能让满眼泪水的小奥古忘记他对达图拉的珍贵记忆。",en:"Nothing or no one could ever make Little Ogrest, his eyes brimming with tears, forget his cherished memory of Dathura."};
descriptions["24028"]={cn:"这戒指证明着，你曾勇于面对十二世界有史以来，最恐怖的危险存在。",en:"This ring is your proof of having braved the most fearful dangers the World of Twelve has ever known."};
descriptions["24029"]={cn:"难以想像一滴泪水能如此危险。小心拿好：一不小心滴落就能轻易淹没整个国家。",en:"Hard to believe that one little tear could be so dangerous. Handle with care: dropping it by accident could easily flood an entire nation."};
descriptions["24031"]={cn:"Yu-Go-Fu! It\'s time to walk miles with your friends to catch them all! All of the Tofus, that is...",en:"Yu-Go-Fu! It\'s time to walk miles with your friends to catch them all! All of the Tofus, that is..."};
descriptions["24034"]={cn:"历尽艰险的你赢得的奖励。你可以用这枚旧奖章兑换钥匙。",en:"You can trade in this hard-won old token for keys."};
descriptions["24037"]={cn:"有了这个强大的戒指就知足吧！一点一滴才是真。",en:"With this great ring, you\'ll be happy being happy! It\'s the little things that count."};
descriptions["24038"]={cn:"这件腰带能够让你释放技能的速度加快，但也会你更加脆弱，所以小心点，别到时候把自己搞的像个兔兔一样慌张。",en:"This belt lets you fire off spells incredibly fast, but it also makes you more fragile. So be careful not to get shot down like a Wodent..."};
descriptions["24039"]={cn:"这双靴子穿起来太舒服了，你觉得非常的满足，然而你的敌人好像不是很稀罕这个。",en:"These shoes are so comfortable, you can\'t help but be satisfied with them. Your enemies might not be quite so content if you decide to give them the boot, though."};
descriptions["24040"]={cn:"它会把你给它的爱都还给你...咸咸的口水喷涌而出。",en:"It will give back all the love you give it... in spurts of salty drool."};
descriptions["24041"]={cn:"看起来很适合你戴。",en:"Luks gud on you."};
descriptions["24042"]={cn:"在造访新地域之前，奥铎迈的斥候会被派去执行侦察任务，装备着这副护腿。",en:"Before visiting new lands, Otomai\'s Scouts are sent on reconnaissance missions, equipped with these very greaves."};
descriptions["24043"]={cn:"就算现在，我依旧可以像切乳酪一样把你们...",en:"Pierce putrid flesh like butter, with one swift stroke!"};
descriptions["24044"]={cn:"巨魔日常训练必备，不过我可不愿意戴上它。配备此肩甲，你最大的AP为 11。",en:"Trools regularly shoulder each other to train. I wouldn\'t try that with these epaulettes, though. With these Epaulettes equipped, your maximum AP is 11."};
descriptions["24045"]={cn:"卡波克用来防止制造机械鸦的时候烧坏自己的胡子。",en:"Kabrok used this to keep from burning his beard while performing various welds on the Korbot."};
descriptions["24046"]={cn:"鸦人最令人不寒而栗的庇护。",en:"One of the most sacred blessings that the Raskaw people can bestow on a young recruit."};
descriptions["24047"]={cn:"曾将在科尔巴商店热卖，现在由于非常稀少变得非常有收藏价值。只有卡波克和一些收藏家还拥有几件。",en:"Once sold in the Kelba shops, it\'s now only available at Kabrok\'s and from the occasional collector."};
descriptions["24048"]={cn:"这根腰带能保证你自己的人身安全，至于其他人嘛，那就不太好说了。",en:"Equipped with this belt, you won\'t be any saner, but you might be belted less."};
descriptions["24049"]={cn:"这靴子可以让你跑超快，即使你的头已经不在脖子上",en:"These boots will let you run very fast, even if you\'ve been beheaded."};
descriptions["24050"]={cn:"是它从你脖子上长出来的，还是你从这个护身符上长出来的？",en:"Did it grow out of your neck, or was it you that grew out of this amulet?"};
descriptions["24051"]={cn:"据说邦塔的贵族阿什·加莱什对于卡牌下了诅咒。无论是谁，只要摸到这套牌，就会变成赌徒。",en:"It\'s said that powerful Bontarian nobleman Ush Galesh put a curse on these cards so that whoever used them would become a gambling addict."};
descriptions["24052"]={cn:"由塔罗迪姆矿石制成，硬度极高！",en:"This helmet was cast from Taroudium ore, so it\'s tremendously tough, especially in cold temperatures!"};
descriptions["24053"]={cn:"This amulet is worn by the Emiw when he goes to answer nature\'s call. It absorbs bad smells.",en:"This amulet is worn by the Emiw when he goes to answer nature\'s call. It absorbs bad smells."};
descriptions["24054"]={cn:"Despite the power contained in this ring, its bearer remains bridled by a strange force. There must no doubt be a way to break the evil spell.",en:"Despite the power contained in this ring, its bearer remains bridled by a strange force. There must no doubt be a way to break the evil spell."};
descriptions["24055"]={cn:"谁是老大？！",en:"Who\'s the boss?!"};
descriptions["24056"]={cn:"The Great Viziw Wabbit can always see a few stabs into the future, and this dagger helps him to use this skill to pewfection.",en:"The Great Viziw Wabbit can always see a few stabs into the future, and this dagger helps him to use this skill to pewfection."};
descriptions["24057"]={cn:"The Lenald Walm Pelt is made completely of Cawotte, it keeps you warm in the winter and is still delicious when next summer comes around.",en:"The Lenald Walm Pelt is made completely of Cawotte, it keeps you warm in the winter and is still delicious when next summer comes around."};
descriptions["24058"]={cn:"这枚戒指携带着Viticultists的气息，证明着你战胜了他。",en:"This ring carries the sign of the Viticultists. It proves you beat them."};
descriptions["24059"]={cn:"先进的工艺制品，其轻便性让你的行动如行云流水。不过一旦受到伤害，却会造成深深的刺痛。",en:"Your movements will be fluid, giving you incomparable combat abilities. But any damage sustained will cause pain that stabs through you like a lance."};
descriptions["24060"]={cn:"虽然这件斗篷很漂亮，但它最多只能让你指挥一团香蕉。话说回来，这其实也不算太寒酸。",en:"While classy, this cloak won\'t let you command much more than a regiment of Citronanas. Then again, that\'s actually not too shabby."};
descriptions["24061"]={cn:"传说中兔皇帝的权力象征！终于到你手上了！你恨不得马上戴上它耀武扬威，对吧？别掩饰了。",en:"The legendary Wa Wabbit\'s Cwown! Finally in your clutches! You know you were hoping to try it on at least once in your life as an adventurer, don\'t pretend you weren\'t."};
descriptions["24062"]={cn:"曾经装备了这个披风的人会隐形。如今只能在布拉克玛旅馆的地毯上看见它了。",en:"There was once a time when this cape made its wearer invisible. Nowadays, it\'s merely used to decorate the floors of Brakmar\'s taverns."};
descriptions["24063"]={cn:"当身处险境时，这柄魔之剑会舍弃防御，释放邪恶的本体，给敌人带来噩梦般得痛苦。",en:"Once it\'s been stuck in an enemy, the protection attached to the sword will come off, unleashing an evil Shushu that will petrify the target with pain."};
descriptions["24064"]={cn:"想穿着这双靴子走路可要费点功夫，它们非常重。不过某种程度上，它们还是能帮助你移动的。",en:"You\'ll have to train pretty seriously to even be able to walk a step in these boots. They\'re really heavy, but somehow they still help you move more easily."};
descriptions["24065"]={cn:"穿着那么闪的腰带，别人当然打不中你。",en:"With such a showy belt around your middle, it shouldn\'t be a mystery why enemies aim so low."};
descriptions["24066"]={cn:"这件道服属于一位欢乐的刺客。据说他去了阿玛克纳，整天幻想着粉色和白色的玫瑰。",en:"This kimono belonged to a degenerate Sram, who was as happy as can be. It is said he set off for Amakna daydreaming of pink and white roses."};
descriptions["24067"]={cn:"当骑士 Marc Daul 误闯军械库，大叫“旅馆老板，标准间！”时，他拿起了这根棒子，因为缺少他梦寐以求的呵口可乐。",en:"When the Iop Marc Daul cried \"Innkeeper, a double!\" when mistakenly entering an armory, he took this stick for lack of the Cacta-Cola that he so desired."};
descriptions["24068"]={cn:"These boots have travelled through the ages on the feet of the proudest warriors, and they\'ve never once crumbled.",en:"These boots have travelled through the ages on the feet of the proudest warriors, and they\'ve never once crumbled."};
descriptions["24069"]={cn:"舒适耐用造型好，谁用谁知道。",en:"This shield offers durable protection and a more natural feel during combat."};
descriptions["24070"]={cn:"如此可爱的设计，连鸟儿都在你身边飞舞了。很棒吧？",en:"With a slightly more charming appearance, you\'ll have the birds all aflutter. Classy, no?"};
descriptions["24071"]={cn:"传奇大师打造的传奇斗篷。",en:"An epic cloak belonging to an epic Cra."};
descriptions["24072"]={cn:"当日落时，记住当地这句充满智慧的口诀：“润唇膏，棕榈魔力，没有伤害。”",en:"When the sun\'s beating down, remember this wise mantra spoken by the locals: \"lip balm, palm charm, no harm.\""};
descriptions["24073"]={cn:"这会让你的肩膀看起来非常美味。",en:"These will make your shoulders look extremely tasty."};
descriptions["24074"]={cn:"最资深的食人族喜欢穿这种胸甲，因为能消除他们在丛林中移动时的障碍。",en:"The most senior Kanniballs like to wear this Breastplate, which removes obstacles as they move through the jungle. A few have tripped and lost an arm."};
descriptions["24075"]={cn:"纯金打造的鳄鱼头镶崁上红宝石眼睛。",en:"A magnificent crocodyl head molded in gold with ruby eyes."};
descriptions["24076"]={cn:"能防御精神攻击。但这功能没什么用，没人想知道会去戴这顶头盔的人脑袋里在想什么。",en:"This protects you from mental attacks. But that\'s not useful. No one wants to know what\'s inside the head of anyone who\'d wear this headgear."};
descriptions["24077"]={cn:"龙鳞绣腰襦，葳蕤自生光。",en:"A belt made of solid dragon scales, shimmering with an iridescent sheen."};
descriptions["24078"]={cn:"传说中这双靴子能让你站在海蓝圆盾上滑行，并持弓在手而不失去准头。",en:"Legend has it that these boots allow you to surf on the Asse Shield, bow in hand, with no loss of precision."};
descriptions["24079"]={cn:"这只强大的戒指有个缺点：穿戴者周围永远会围绕着一股清凉的微风。",en:"This powerful ring has one disadvantage: its wearer is permanently surrounded by a slight cool breeze."};
descriptions["24080"]={cn:"既奢华且强大，这件别致的肩甲因其两颗红宝石而得名。",en:"Luxurious and formidable, these classy epaulettes get their name from the two rubies set into them."};
descriptions["24081"]={cn:"没有任何事物或任何人，能让满眼泪水的小奥古忘记他对达图拉的珍贵记忆。",en:"Nothing or no one could ever make Little Ogrest, his eyes brimming with tears, forget his cherished memory of Dathura."};
descriptions["24082"]={cn:"芬里斯将风度和举止教授给了酷洛宇宙的居民。正是在他的影响下，女人们会连续几个小时独占浴室...",en:"Fhenris teaches the Krosmoz\'s inhabitants about style and bearing. It\'s his influence that makes ladies monopolize the bathroom for hours on end..."};
descriptions["24083"]={cn:"只有我，最摇摆！",en:"Gettin\' jiggly wit it!"};
descriptions["24084"]={cn:"Boots which help protect from ultra strong heat, but that also reinforce foot odor.",en:"Boots which help protect from ultra strong heat, but that also reinforce foot odor."};
descriptions["24085"]={cn:"This insignia was mighty hard to obtain, but the prestige and efficiency it brings you make it worth the wait!",en:"This insignia was mighty hard to obtain, but the prestige and efficiency it brings you make it worth the wait!"};
descriptions["24086"]={cn:"品质超凡的胸甲，由阿斯图布的奥铎麦门徒提供。别弄丢了，奥铎麦门徒以后还会需要这件胸甲！",en:"An extraordinary piece of armor, given to you as a reward by Otomai\'s Disciple in Astrub. He promised you another mission, in exchange for which he\'ll reward you even more. Don\'t forget to go back and see him!"};
descriptions["24087"]={cn:"坠饰里流出美味粘稠的蜂蜜，但现在它看起来更像冰冻蜂蜜。放心，不会流的你全身，只会流到上半身。",en:"Sticky and delicious honey once flowed from this amulet, but now it looks more like iced honey. One thing is sure: it won\'t leak all over your torso."};
descriptions["24088"]={cn:"把戒指戴在不同的手指上会有不同的效果。这些细节都写在一份神秘的古代手稿中，但不幸的是，它似乎无法翻译。",en:"Putting this ring on different fingers gets different results. The details were all written down in a mysterious ancient manuscript, but unfortunately, it seems to be untranslatable."};
descriptions["24089"]={cn:"一场豪赌的产物，赢的那一方取走了这条闪亮的腰带。",en:"This magnificent belt is the result of a mad bet to restore one of the most beautiful belts ever created in Amakna: the Powerful Dazzling Belt! Pakape Promethe won the contest."};
descriptions["24090"]={cn:"曾经属于熊猫武僧首领张·冰雪美酒。因为缺少实验志愿者，他不得已只能自己来试用斗笠，测试它作为尿壶的隐藏功能。",en:"The Solomonk used to belong to an old Pandawa chief who was an expert in laxative potions. Lacking willing subjects, he had to test the potions himself, and used it as a chamber pot."};
descriptions["24091"]={cn:"哈利是个很有智慧的老人，喜欢光着脚钓鱼。终于有一天，在某个漫长的夏日的傍晚，他把自己的靴子忘记在萨弗基亚的码头上了。",en:"Harry was an old wise man who loved to fish with bare feet. Inevitably, after a long summer day, he forgot his boots on the Sufokian docks."};
descriptions["24092"]={cn:"柔软的披风，可以不穿内衣贴身穿着！一种展现男子汉气概的优雅方式...",en:"This cape has a reputation for legendary softness, which means you can wear it without any underwear! An elegant way to expose yourself..."};
descriptions["24093"]={cn:"这面盾牌中含有海水的成分，让你在战斗中感觉清凉爽快，特别是女朋友没在边上观战的时候。",en:"This magnificent shield contains a few drops of seawater. Not only does it bring good luck but it can also be used as a flask."};
descriptions["24094"]={cn:"把戒指戴在不同的手指上会有不同的效果。这些细节都写在一份神秘的古代手稿中，但不幸的是，它似乎无法翻译。",en:"Putting this ring on different fingers gets different results. The details were all written down in a mysterious ancient manuscript, but unfortunately, it seems to be untranslatable."};
descriptions["24095"]={cn:"When your enemies see these boots, they\'ll feel like rats on a sinking ship.",en:"When your enemies see these boots, they\'ll feel like rats on a sinking ship."};
descriptions["24096"]={cn:"魔眼的残留嵌入了这个护符，戴上它的人会在每场战斗之前获得一个强力的光环。",en:"Flaxhid\'s remains encrusted into this Talisman give off an aura of power that adorns its bearer before each combat."};
descriptions["24097"]={cn:"绑在你的手上，妈妈再也不用担心我会丢钥匙了。",en:"The perfect tool to keep track of your keys and always have them to hand."};
descriptions["24098"]={cn:"这副肩甲久经沙场。虽然不如从前那么坚固，但是如果你不想武器报废的话，最好不要用力砍它。",en:"These epaulettes have seen more than one battle. They may not look too sturdy, but best not to hit them too hard if you want to keep your weapon."};
descriptions["24099"]={cn:"这件胸甲吞噬主人的灵魂，让他失去七情六欲。",en:"This breastplate devours its wearer\'s soul, making them completely invulnerable to blows and emotions."};
descriptions["24100"]={cn:"我的身体，裹着受伤的绷带，\n我的伤口，被安全地包裹着，\n在风中自由地飘动，\n我表现出疯狂，而你将会哭泣！\n所以我悄然地离去，像一个可怕的畜生，\n我的手上有你的血，我的脚上有你的鞋！\n“憎恨”的波否，一名狂战士以及闲暇时的吟游诗人。",en:"My body is covered in Wounded Straps,\nMy injuries, though, are safely wrapped,\nIn the wind they are freely flowing,\nI show my madness, and you\'ll be crying!\nAnd so I leave, like a horrid brute,\nOn my hands your blood, on my feet your boots!\n— Polver \"The Hate\", Sacrier and bard in his spare time."};
descriptions["24101"]={cn:"这件披风可遇而不可求，不过既然你已经穿上了说明也不是那么难以获得。",en:"This cloak may be the physical manifestation of luck itself, but the fact that you\'re wearing it wasn\'t left to chance."};
descriptions["24102"]={cn:"这根指针古往今来一直受到人们的喜爱。有些人甚至在做这个任务的时候就已经疯了。",en:"This hand is respected throughout the ages. Some have even gone mad in their quest to get their hands on it."};
descriptions["24103"]={cn:"N.I.O.是一个每周日晚上都会在阿斯图布下水道开会的委员会。没有人知道每个字母代表什么，因为成员都是昆虫爱好者，喜欢把秘密藏在心中，可能代表着昆虫的零食，药品，亦或是更加恐怖的东西。",en:"The N.I.O. is a committee which meets every Sunday evening in the depths of the Astrub Sewers. No one knows what the acronym stands for, because the members of the committee, who were big insect lovers, took the secret to their graves after confusing their favorite treat, the Phix, with the fatal Bhug! It looks good on you though, and that\'s what matters."};
descriptions["24104"]={cn:"这件护肩来自一个古老的国度，据说它曾经的主人是一个精通战争艺术和秘法的猴子国王。",en:"These epaulettes come from an ancient kingdom, and it\'s said they belonged to a Monkey King, an expert in martial arts and master of secret bō techniques."};
descriptions["24105"]={cn:"它是猴王的一种特殊变体，月之肩甲的效果并没有减少。",en:"A variant of the very specialized version originating from the Monkey King, these Moon Epaulettes are no less effective."};
descriptions["24106"]={cn:"根据传说，暴风腰带是很久以前由最有名的凯拉所制作的，但这一条腰带可能只是食人族的仿造品。",en:"According to legend, the Belt of the Winds was created a long time ago by the most popular Cra. But this one is probably just an inferior copy slapped together by a Kanniball smuggler."};
descriptions["24107"]={cn:"These daggers get their name from the fact they attack their owner at night. They are always sharpened once per decade. When acquiring these ancient weapons imbued with dark magic, it\'s always wiser to acquire a used pair so their behavior can be observed properly.",en:"These daggers get their name from the fact they attack their owner at night. They are always sharpened once per decade. When acquiring these ancient weapons imbued with dark magic, it\'s always wiser to acquire a used pair so their behavior can be observed properly."};
descriptions["24108"]={cn:"据说，奥铎迈的门徒穿着这双鞋周游十二世界，寻找宝藏和生物...",en:"It is said that Otomai\'s pilgrims wore these shoes to travel the World of Twelve in search of treasures and creatures..."};
descriptions["24109"]={cn:"得到这东西的战斗之艰辛，堪称你活到现在之最：活到现在。",en:"You got this during the most difficult fight of your life: your life."};
descriptions["24110"]={cn:"这枚宝贵的虹色龙蛋来自诺戈翼龙，一条过去的幼龙。",en:"The precious Prismatic Dofus of Nogord Wungleezared, a minor dragon from the past."};
descriptions["24111"]={cn:"相传一名从事军火事业叫“尼东·史塔克”的守护者，设计了一件能让使用者飞行的装甲，其能量由胸甲中间的红宝石提供。",en:"It\'s said that a Feca called \"Noty Strak\" who was in the business of making weapons had the idea of creating a full set of armor that lets its wearer fly, taking its power from a ruby placed in the middle of the chest."};
descriptions["24112"]={cn:"这件黑暗披风属于一位邪恶之主，其为另 8 名邪众之首。所到之处暗夜随行，死亡之声由众口尖啸而出。",en:"A dark coat that belonged to an evil lord, leader of 8 other accomplices. The night walked with them, and death cried forth from their mouths."};
descriptions["24113"]={cn:"这条护符曾经属於一位掌握了四种原初元素能量的光能法师，但显然造化（或奥古）弄人啊。",en:"This amulet once belonged to a Huppermage who mastered the four primordial elemental energies. Apparently, fate (or Ogrest) played a trick on him."};
descriptions["24114"]={cn:"这戒指证明着，你曾勇于面对十二世界有史以来，最恐怖的危险存在。",en:"This ring is your proof of having braved the most fearful dangers the World of Twelve has ever known."};
descriptions["24115"]={cn:"很久以前，人们相信智慧是金。现在，这个护符汇集了世上所有的智慧。",en:"Many moons ago, people used to say that wisdom was golden.\nNow the only wisdom left in this World is embedded deep inside this amulet."};
descriptions["24116"]={cn:"强大的项链，由龙鳞的残片制成，能击退敌人的精锐。",en:"This splendid amulet, made from Dreggon remains, does a pretty impressive job fighting off the majority of your enemies."};
descriptions["24117"]={cn:"举起手来...这只戒指有点蹊跷！",en:"Hold up... There\'s something funny about this ring!"};
descriptions["24118"]={cn:"制定法律，盖上印章，在兔皇面前显摆！",en:"Affix your seal, impose your laws, and pose in front of the Wa!"};
descriptions["24119"]={cn:"让你登高山如履平地。",en:"These boots allow plain sailing on the plains of Mount Zinit."};
descriptions["24120"]={cn:"这里放一个瞬移光环，那里放一个瞬移光环，好了你不用出示护照就能出国了！",en:"Now you can try to get through customs without being stopped! But don\'t get too cocky..."};
descriptions["24121"]={cn:"Unfortunately, this one can\'t boast +20, but they say it\'s a relic handed down for generations, which has to count for something.",en:"Unfortunately, this one can\'t boast +20, but they say it\'s a relic handed down for generations, which has to count for something."};
descriptions["24122"]={cn:"当熊猫武僧喝多了之后会动不动就脱下腰带。好吧，实际上他们经常光着屁股。",en:"This is the famous belt that Pandawans tend to take off when they\'ve drunk too much. Let\'s just say they don\'t wear it too often."};
descriptions["24123"]={cn:"保护秀发免受伤害。",en:"This hat will probably give you hat hair."};
descriptions["24124"]={cn:"很显然马加罗夫再也不用哼哼了。这毫无意义。就像你一样。",en:"This must be the hat Magalouf was talking about in his rhyme \'eenie meenie hatty ho.\' This information is completely useless. Much like yourself."};
descriptions["24125"]={cn:"在下雨天里也能让你保持干燥爽洁。",en:"This cloak will keep you dry on those rainy days."};
descriptions["24126"]={cn:"即便是再冷的笑话，它也会鼓掌。至少你再也不用担心讲完笑话后的冷场了...",en:"This cloak will applaud anything, even a badly made joke. As least you won\'t have to endure that awkward silence after yours anymore..."};
descriptions["24127"]={cn:"早就告诉你们了，这当然不会是最后一件...",en:"We told you it wouldn\'t be the last..."};
descriptions["24128"]={cn:"Before you wear this armor, there is one condition: you have to be able to say \"Sue shooed Shushus by the sea shore\" without swallowing your tongue.",en:"Before you wear this armor, there is one condition: you have to be able to say \"Sue shooed Shushus by the sea shore\" without swallowing your tongue."};
descriptions["24129"]={cn:"多亏了这对肩甲，你能将正义的种子散播到贫瘠的地区。或者你也可以变成一个不断追求力量的疯子，满脑子想着自私自利的正义。",en:"Thanks to these epaulettes, you can spread justice to the impoverished. Or you can become a power-thirsty lunatic with his own selfish ideas about justice."};
descriptions["24130"]={cn:"此升华能装进史诗物品，提升穿戴者的能力。",en:"This rune fits into an epic item to increase the wearer\'s stats."};
descriptions["24131"]={cn:"此升华能装进史诗物品，提升穿戴者的能力。",en:"This rune fits into an epic item to increase the wearer\'s stats."};
descriptions["24132"]={cn:"此升华能装进史诗物品，提升穿戴者的能力。",en:"This rune fits into an epic item to increase the wearer\'s stats."};
descriptions["24133"]={cn:"此升华能装进史诗物品，提升穿戴者的能力。",en:"This rune fits into an epic item to increase the wearer\'s stats."};
descriptions["24134"]={cn:"此升华能装进史诗物品，提升穿戴者的能力。",en:"This rune fits into an epic item to increase the wearer\'s stats."};
descriptions["24135"]={cn:"此升华能装进遗物物品，提升穿戴者的能力。",en:"This sublimation fits into a relic item to increase the wearer\'s stats."};
descriptions["24136"]={cn:"此升华能装进遗物物品，提升穿戴者的能力。",en:"This sublimation fits into a relic item to increase the wearer\'s stats."};
descriptions["24137"]={cn:"此升华能装进遗物物品，提升穿戴者的能力。",en:"This sublimation fits into a relic item to increase the wearer\'s stats."};
descriptions["24138"]={cn:"此升华能装进遗物物品，提升穿戴者的能力。",en:"This sublimation fits into a relic item to increase the wearer\'s stats."};
descriptions["24140"]={cn:"Laying down your weapons isn\'t usually much fun, which is why this manual will teach you to pick them up and use them.",en:"Laying down your weapons isn\'t usually much fun, which is why this manual will teach you to pick them up and use them."};
descriptions["24141"]={cn:"If you\'re ever lucky enough to see this seal stamped on a piece of equipment, you can be sure that the craftsman who made it is a very great master indeed.",en:"If you\'re ever lucky enough to see this seal stamped on a piece of equipment, you can be sure that the craftsman who made it is a very great master indeed."};
descriptions["24142"]={cn:"Mihmosa likes to start a fight by waving his staff around to intimidate his victims. He loves seeing them run away, trembling like leaves and with their tails between their legs.",en:"Mihmosa likes to start a fight by waving his staff around to intimidate his victims. He loves seeing them run away, trembling like leaves and with their tails between their legs."};
descriptions["24143"]={cn:"Mihmosa likes to start a fight by waving his staff around to intimidate his victims. He loves seeing them run away, trembling like leaves and with their tails between their legs.",en:"Mihmosa likes to start a fight by waving his staff around to intimidate his victims. He loves seeing them run away, trembling like leaves and with their tails between their legs."};
descriptions["24144"]={cn:"这斗蓬看似普通，但确有着神奇的力量！披着它的人能在没走路不看路的人面前隐形，太神奇了！",en:"This cloak may look ordinary, but it has magical powers! It will make its wearer invisible to anyone who isn\'t looking their way. Impressive!"};
descriptions["24145"]={cn:"这斗蓬看似普通，但确有着神奇的力量！披着它的人能在没走路不看路的人面前隐形，太神奇了！",en:"This cloak may look ordinary, but it has magical powers! It will make its wearer invisible to anyone who isn\'t looking their way. Impressive!"};
descriptions["24146"]={cn:"很久以前，人们相信智慧是金。现在，这个护符汇集了世上所有的智慧。",en:"Many moons ago, people used to say that wisdom was golden.\nNow the only wisdom left in this World is embedded deep inside this amulet."};
descriptions["24147"]={cn:"让你登高山如履平地。",en:"These boots allow plain sailing on the plains of Mount Zinit."};
descriptions["24148"]={cn:"在下雨天里也能让你保持干燥爽洁。",en:"This cloak will keep you dry on those rainy days."};
descriptions["24149"]={cn:"保护秀发免受伤害。",en:"This hat will probably give you hat hair."};
descriptions["24150"]={cn:"即便是再冷的笑话，它也会鼓掌。至少你再也不用担心讲完笑话后的冷场了...",en:"This cloak will applaud anything, even a badly made joke. As least you won\'t have to endure that awkward silence after yours anymore..."};
descriptions["24151"]={cn:"即便是再冷的笑话，它也会鼓掌。至少你再也不用担心讲完笑话后的冷场了...",en:"This cloak will applaud anything, even a badly made joke. As least you won\'t have to endure that awkward silence after yours anymore..."};
descriptions["24152"]={cn:"这位老财奴变成豆芙时还挺可爱的。但，还是...",en:"This old penny-pincher is actually kind of cute as a Tofu. Still, though..."};
descriptions["24153"]={cn:"你通常不会喜欢绿色的动物玩偶，但这可是阿玛莉雅！",en:"You don\'t normally like green stuffed animals, but this is Amalia we\'re talking about!"};
descriptions["24154"]={cn:"这个豆芙玩偶会像爱之箭一样射穿你的心。",en:"This stuffed Tofu will pierce your heart like an arrow of love."};
descriptions["24155"]={cn:"晚上抱着这个动物玩偶的话，会让你跟骑士一样勇敢。",en:"This stuffed animal makes you as bold as a Iop when you cuddle up with it at night."};
descriptions["24156"]={cn:"使用后会启动或关闭终结技。此物品不可堆叠。发动时会从启动的终结技里随机发动一个。",en:"Using this will activate or deactivate the Finisher. The item is not consumed. Random selection among all active Finishers."};
descriptions["24157"]={cn:"With this helmet on your head, you may find yourself starting to collect all kinds of things... Strange things. To say the least.",en:"With this helmet on your head, you may find yourself starting to collect all kinds of things... Strange things. To say the least."};
descriptions["24158"]={cn:"This mask will make you look like a psychopath.",en:"This mask will make you look like a psychopath."};
descriptions["24159"]={cn:"No other cloak is as loyal as this one. Some say it can even lead you back towards the light if you\'re in a dark place.",en:"No other cloak is as loyal as this one. Some say it can even lead you back towards the light if you\'re in a dark place."};
descriptions["24160"]={cn:"This shield will protect you for a while from the destruction that each of us must face in the end.",en:"This shield will protect you for a while from the destruction that each of us must face in the end."};
descriptions["24161"]={cn:"This Tofu flaps its wings so fast that you\'d almost think you were flying when you get on its back. You\'re not, of course, but it\'s still worth a ride!",en:"This Tofu flaps its wings so fast that you\'d almost think you were flying when you get on its back. You\'re not, of course, but it\'s still worth a ride!"};
descriptions["24162"]={cn:"This Bow Meow is so cute that you can\'t help wanting to... climb on its back?! How absurd!",en:"This Bow Meow is so cute that you can\'t help wanting to... climb on its back?! How absurd!"};
descriptions["24163"]={cn:"This Boon is the perfect companion for brand-new adventures. Its extreme attentiveness and long-winded explanations can get a bit annoying over time, though.",en:"This Boon is the perfect companion for brand-new adventures. Its extreme attentiveness and long-winded explanations can get a bit annoying over time, though."};
descriptions["24167"]={cn:"This Tofu skin has a tendency to jump on anything that moves in order to fuse with it... And it might well succeed!",en:"This Tofu skin has a tendency to jump on anything that moves in order to fuse with it... And it might well succeed!"};
descriptions["24168"]={cn:"This Bow Meow skin reflects all your inner chaos.",en:"This Bow Meow skin reflects all your inner chaos."};
descriptions["24169"]={cn:"This Boon skin loves Kokonuts with chocolate, but never feed it any after midnight!",en:"This Boon skin loves Kokonuts with chocolate, but never feed it any after midnight!"};
descriptions["24170"]={cn:"为了奖励你在地下城的杰出排名，季末宝箱里放了给你的奖赏。打开来看看你得到了什么！",en:"The End-of-Season Chest contains your rewards for being ranked among the best in a dungeon. Open it to find out what you\'ve won!"};
descriptions["24171"]={cn:"为了奖励你在地下城的杰出排名，季末宝箱里放了给你的奖赏。打开来看看你得到了什么！",en:"The End-of-Season Chest contains your rewards for being ranked among the best in a dungeon. Open it to find out what you\'ve won!"};
