descriptions["24193"]={cn:"你可以将 M 战警绑定至你的帐号并在战斗中使用。注意！除去个别特殊情况，这项操作无法被取消。",en:"This item enables you to link this sidekick to your account and use it in combat. Careful! This action cannot be undone, except under certain circumstances."};
descriptions["24194"]={cn:"Don\'t forget your underwear when wearing this costume!",en:"Don\'t forget your underwear when wearing this costume!"};
descriptions["24195"]={cn:"This costume is perfect for terrorizing the neighborhood children whenever they come asking for candy.",en:"This costume is perfect for terrorizing the neighborhood children whenever they come asking for candy."};
descriptions["24199"]={cn:"Feeling blue? Failed the achievement again? Come and grab a coffee!",en:"Feeling blue? Failed the achievement again? Come and grab a coffee!"};
