descriptions["24220"]={cn:"此庇护袋外观为你完成一个十二世界挑战后的奖励！",en:"This Haven Bag Kit is your reward for completing a World of Twelve challenge!"};
descriptions["24221"]={cn:"This must be the hat Magalouf was talking about in his rhyme \'eenie meenie hatty ho.\' This information is completely useless. Just like you.",en:"This must be the hat Magalouf was talking about in his rhyme \'eenie meenie hatty ho.\' This information is completely useless. Just like you."};
descriptions["24222"]={cn:"We did say that it definitely wouldn\'t be the last...",en:"We did say that it definitely wouldn\'t be the last..."};
descriptions["24223"]={cn:"当熊猫武僧喝多了之后会动不动就脱下腰带。好吧，实际上他们经常光着屁股。",en:"This is the famous belt that Pandawans tend to take off when they\'ve drunk too much. Let\'s just say they don\'t wear it too often."};
descriptions["24240"]={cn:"By wearing this costume, you\'ll feel that you can reach all your objectives, as distant as they may be.",en:"By wearing this costume, you\'ll feel that you can reach all your objectives, as distant as they may be."};
descriptions["24241"]={cn:"Relive your childhood by throwing on this costume with the traits of young Ogrest.",en:"Relive your childhood by throwing on this costume with the traits of young Ogrest."};
descriptions["24242"]={cn:"Put on this hood and you\'ll have all of Oropo\'s gravitas. However, you still won\'t know who\'s hidden underneath it.",en:"Put on this hood and you\'ll have all of Oropo\'s gravitas. However, you still won\'t know who\'s hidden underneath it."};
descriptions["24243"]={cn:"These colors suit you ravishingly!",en:"These colors suit you ravishingly!"};
descriptions["24244"]={cn:"This Boowolf skin will make a god out of you!",en:"This Boowolf skin will make a god out of you!"};
descriptions["24245"]={cn:"This Pingwii is so fresh!",en:"This Pingwii is so fresh!"};
descriptions["24246"]={cn:"Our precious gifts! They\'ve been stolen!",en:"Our precious gifts! They\'ve been stolen!"};
descriptions["24247"]={cn:"使用后会启动或关闭终结技。此物品不可堆叠。发动时会从启动的终结技里随机发动一个。",en:"Using this will activate or deactivate the Finisher. The item is not consumed. Random selection among all active Finishers."};
descriptions["24248"]={cn:"谁说木乃伊只能穿着一身破布的？有了这样外观，南瓜节最狂的就是你！",en:"Whoever said that mummies only wore rags? You\'ll be fit to be tied at Al Howin wearing this smashing kit!"};
descriptions["24249"]={cn:"此庇护袋外观为你完成一个十二世界挑战后的奖励！",en:"This Haven Bag Kit is your reward for completing a World of Twelve challenge!"};
