descriptions["24252"]={cn:"使穿戴者心境平和地接受整个世界。",en:"This pendant helps its wearer make peace with the World around him."};
descriptions["24253"]={cn:"穿上这件胸甲后你觉得精疲力尽...它能将你的生命能量吸收殆尽。",en:"It\'s normal to feel exhausted after wearing this breastplate...\nIt sucks the life right out of you."};
descriptions["24254"]={cn:"它们不从脖子而是从肩膀吸血。",en:"Instead of going for the neck, these epaulettes suck blood from the shoulders."};
descriptions["24255"]={cn:"如果戒指发出喘息声，不用紧张。因为有一个饱受折磨的海盗灵魂寄居其上。",en:"If your finger starts breathing by itself when you put this ring on, relax: it\'s just the soul of a tortured pirate who\'s been trapped inside for several decades."};
descriptions["24256"]={cn:"你说什么？你昨天刚见过？他们已经死了20多年了...！",en:"What do you mean, you saw them just yesterday? They\'ve been dead for twenty yeeeaaars...!"};
descriptions["24257"]={cn:"When this hammer hits the ground, a nauseating stench fills the vicinity. It\'s in your best interests to learn how to fight from a distance, and fast!",en:"When this hammer hits the ground, a nauseating stench fills the vicinity. It\'s in your best interests to learn how to fight from a distance, and fast!"};
descriptions["24259"]={cn:"This Godron is so charming he could be a prince!",en:"This Godron is so charming he could be a prince!"};
descriptions["24260"]={cn:"Instead of guarding a dungeon, this Godron maintains order and tranquility.",en:"Instead of guarding a dungeon, this Godron maintains order and tranquility."};
descriptions["24261"]={cn:"This Godron doesn\'t just bite: He claws and breathes fire too! What a beast!",en:"This Godron doesn\'t just bite: He claws and breathes fire too! What a beast!"};
descriptions["24262"]={cn:"There\'s nothing special about this Godron, but thanks to you, he is very nice!",en:"There\'s nothing special about this Godron, but thanks to you, he is very nice!"};
descriptions["24263"]={cn:"This Godron has learned some filthy habits from you!",en:"This Godron has learned some filthy habits from you!"};
descriptions["24264"]={cn:"If you hadn\'t fed it, this Godron would have found something to eat in any case!",en:"If you hadn\'t fed it, this Godron would have found something to eat in any case!"};
descriptions["24265"]={cn:"This bandage protected a living-dead creature, so it\'s bound to cure what ails the living!",en:"This bandage protected a living-dead creature, so it\'s bound to cure what ails the living!"};
descriptions["24266"]={cn:"这些是用来填满你的口袋的！",en:"These are meant for stuffing your pockets!"};
descriptions["24267"]={cn:"累积经验用的一些东西！",en:"Here\'s something to fill up on experience!"};
descriptions["24268"]={cn:"这些将帮助你享受胜利的甘甜！",en:"These will help you savor sweet victory!"};
descriptions["24271"]={cn:"最多可容纳四个人的桌子。",en:"A table that can host up to four people."};
descriptions["24272"]={cn:"这张床保证了长稳的睡眠。",en:"This bed guarantees eternal sleep."};
descriptions["24273"]={cn:"这个橱柜能存放绷带而且不会皱掉。",en:"This cupboard stores bandages without them wrinkling."};
descriptions["24274"]={cn:"比起隐藏背后的东西，这个屏风更容易引起注意。",en:"This screen is more likely to catch the eye than hide whatever\'s behind it."};
descriptions["24275"]={cn:"这种植物的叶子也可以当扇子来用。",en:"This plant\'s leaves can also be used as a fan."};
descriptions["24276"]={cn:"而你玩的是你那有着红眼睛的金甲虫！",en:"And you play your golden Scarab with red eyes!"};
descriptions["24277"]={cn:"You\'ll be able to pray so hard Tow Keyo won\'t believe it.",en:"You\'ll be able to pray so hard Tow Keyo won\'t believe it."};
descriptions["24278"]={cn:"A lamp used to bring light to an ancient tomb.",en:"A lamp used to bring light to an ancient tomb."};
descriptions["24279"]={cn:"There\'s nothing being transformed into a mummy to scare kids.",en:"There\'s nothing being transformed into a mummy to scare kids."};
descriptions["24280"]={cn:"It was a bit nippy out, I\'m staying in my sarcophagus, and you can stay jealous!\n(Caution: The transformation is lost if the character moves.)",en:"It was a bit nippy out, I\'m staying in my sarcophagus, and you can stay jealous!\n(Caution: The transformation is lost if the character moves.)"};
descriptions["24285"]={cn:"Howl wildly: at the full moon, at your ancestors, or at all the injustices in this world. Then it\'ll all be better!",en:"Howl wildly: at the full moon, at your ancestors, or at all the injustices in this world. Then it\'ll all be better!"};
descriptions["24287"]={cn:"在矿洞里缺炸弹时，可以用这件披风代替。点燃了就快跑！",en:"If ever you\'re running low on dynamite in the mines, this cape\'s got your back. Light it and run!"};
descriptions["24288"]={cn:"把自己伪装成死人，在即将加入死者行列的人中间悄无声息地行走。",en:"Disguise yourself as dead to walk harmlessly among those who will soon join the dead."};
descriptions["24289"]={cn:"穿上这件带翅膀的服装，你就可以飞了！",en:"It\'s up, up and away for you with this winged costume!"};
descriptions["24290"]={cn:"穿上你最漂亮的皮毛，把每个人都去蹭一下，这就是艾卡菲利精神！",en:"Don your most beautiful fur to rub everyone against the grain, that too is the Ecaflip spirit!"};
descriptions["24291"]={cn:"你追踪、狩猎并对制作这套服装的野兽进行了加工。它像皮革一样坚硬，但你把它的皮晒得很好！",en:"You tracked, hunted and trepanned the beast that was used to make this costume. It was tough as leather, but you tanned its hide quite nicely!"};
descriptions["24292"]={cn:"Shiny armor made from the remains of powerful monsters. Wearing it shows your tenacity in combat.",en:"Shiny armor made from the remains of powerful monsters. Wearing it shows your tenacity in combat."};
descriptions["24293"]={cn:"This slightly ugly pet loves chewing, but won\'t chew the fat for the fun of it. Be careful, though: You never know what it\'ll swallow.",en:"This slightly ugly pet loves chewing, but won\'t chew the fat for the fun of it. Be careful, though: You never know what it\'ll swallow."};
descriptions["24294"]={cn:"This Dragominus skin looks like the largest of dragons!",en:"This Dragominus skin looks like the largest of dragons!"};
descriptions["24295"]={cn:"使用后会启动或关闭终结技。此物品不可堆叠。发动时会从启动的终结技里随机发动一个。",en:"Using this will activate or deactivate the Finisher. The item is not consumed. Random selection among all active Finishers."};
descriptions["24296"]={cn:"使用后会启动或关闭终结技。此物品不可堆叠。发动时会从启动的终结技里随机发动一个。",en:"Using this will activate or deactivate the Finisher. The item is not consumed. Random selection among all active Finishers."};
descriptions["24297"]={cn:"You\'d have to have put your brain on ice to turn a snowman into a Haven Bag.",en:"You\'d have to have put your brain on ice to turn a snowman into a Haven Bag."};
descriptions["24298"]={cn:"Certainly a niche market, but any Ouginak will swear that these Haven Bags make even a night in the doghouse better.",en:"Certainly a niche market, but any Ouginak will swear that these Haven Bags make even a night in the doghouse better."};
descriptions["24299"]={cn:"这枚戒指极度渴望一根能戴上去的手指，甚至途中还成为了位好老师。",en:"This ring is desperately looking for a finger to slide onto. It even became a great teacher during its quest."};
descriptions["24300"]={cn:"天啊！这头盔真是仿JoJo做的吗！？",en:"Holy smokes! Is this helmet really a JoJo reference!?"};
descriptions["24301"]={cn:"这根针能插入任何地方，即使是最细小的裂缝都行，很适合织补袜子！",en:"This needle can fit anywhere, even in the tiniest of cracks. Handy for darning socks!"};
descriptions["24302"]={cn:"毕竟，这就只是双靴子。",en:"After all, it\'s only a simple pair of boots."};
descriptions["24303"]={cn:"别盯着这项练发出的光太久，不然可能会不再能够晒太阳。",en:"Don\'t stare at the light coming from this amulet for too long, or you might no longer be able to stand sunlight."};
descriptions["24304"]={cn:"“真是副好肩甲。”\n“不，这是我兄弟。”",en:"\"What nice epaulettes you have.\"\n\"No, that\'s my brother.\""};
descriptions["24305"]={cn:"这件披风的颜色现在都没了，而在某个时期曾具有彩虹所有的颜色，并且最一开始时是橘色的。",en:"This cape has lost all color, but it had been every color of the rainbow at one point. Initially, it was orange."};
descriptions["24306"]={cn:"最好还要配上红色紧身衣和一根雪茄。",en:"A waist-cincher to be worn, preferably with a close-fitting red suit while smoking a cigar."};
descriptions["24307"]={cn:"两只手都不够挥舞这把剑。",en:"You\'ll need more than two arms to wield this sword."};
descriptions["24308"]={cn:"据说这是一位不死的无头骑士所用的盾。",en:"It is said that this shield was borne by a headless knight who could not die."};
descriptions["24309"]={cn:"骑士该知道如何使用他们的头脑！",en:"Iops should know how to use their heads!"};
descriptions["24310"]={cn:"这条腰带投射出比现实还真实的巨大立体投影。",en:"This belt projects titanic holograms that are realer than real."};
descriptions["24311"]={cn:"谁知道呢？说不定你换的不是胸甲，而是把意识换到另一个身体里了...",en:"Who knows? Instead of changing breastplate, you might simply have moved your consciousness to a different body..."};
descriptions["24312"]={cn:"向下扎根的徽章。",en:"An emblem to put down roots."};
descriptions["24313"]={cn:"打结的徽章。",en:"An emblem to forge ties."};
descriptions["24314"]={cn:"散发生命气息的徽章。",en:"An emblem to breathe life."};
descriptions["24315"]={cn:"登上顶端的徽章。",en:"An emblem to attain the tip top."};
descriptions["24316"]={cn:"打开包裹，看看里面的礼物吧！",en:"Open this pouch and behold the gift within!"};
descriptions["24317"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。\n打开它只需要两秒！",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["24319"]={cn:"从高处跳进干草推时很有用。",en:"This helmet will be very useful when plunging from up high into haystacks."};
descriptions["24320"]={cn:"曾经属于有史以来最伟大的龙鸟骑士Granne，上面有着他打滑的每一道痕迹。",en:"This belt was once worn by the greatest Dragoturkey rider of all times, Granne. It bears the marks of his many skids."};
descriptions["24321"]={cn:"有 23 种样式的披风，全都多少有相似之处。",en:"A cape that comes in 23 styles, all of which have more or less the same features."};
descriptions["24322"]={cn:"超・级・靴・超・级・靴・超・级・靴",en:"SUPER. BOOTS. SUPER. BOOTS. SUPER. BOOTS."};
descriptions["24323"]={cn:"彻底程序化的戒指，每一层金属都有命名。",en:"An entirely procedural ring, whose every layer of metal has been named."};
descriptions["24324"]={cn:"就跟其它人一样，史坦利从荧幕看到数字上下跑动，然后听到了一道声音。",en:"Stanley was like everyone else; he saw numbers scrolling across his screen. Then, he heard a voice."};
descriptions["24325"]={cn:"这把剑能在最近的村庄换到多种商品。",en:"This sword can be traded for various goods in the nearest village."};
descriptions["24326"]={cn:"这条项链有只泡在福马林里的鼠小弟，真棒...",en:"This amulet contains a Ratou preserved in formalin. Lovely..."};
descriptions["24327"]={cn:"能变为多种外型，但通常用做家具。",en:"Epaulettes that can take on quirky shapes, but often that of various items of furniture."};
descriptions["24328"]={cn:"某天...你进来了！当然，是进来这副胸甲。",en:"And one day... You got in! Into this breastplate, that is."};
descriptions["24329"]={cn:"一具空荡的残骸，其内空无一物...似乎会在营火旁复生。",en:"An empty carcass, with nothing inside... It seems to come to life next to campfires."};
descriptions["24330"]={cn:"要拿到这双可真是非常不容易。",en:"You had a BAD TIME getting these boots."};
descriptions["24331"]={cn:"这件物品探索着共有的意识，直到抵达我们所有人内在的邪恶根部为止。",en:"This item explores shared consciousness until it reaches the root of the evil within us all."};
descriptions["24332"]={cn:"到达顶端的人够格戴上这徽章。",en:"Those who reach the summit are worthy of wearing this emblem."};
descriptions["24333"]={cn:"散发着眩目的神奇绿光。",en:"An emblem that shines a blinding, supernatural green."};
descriptions["24334"]={cn:"打开包裹，看看里面的礼物吧！",en:"Open this pouch and behold the gift within!"};
descriptions["24336"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。\n打开它只需要两秒！",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
