descriptions["24680"]={cn:"手中有了这把剑，你在对战友演讲时会使自己受到鼓舞。",en:"With this sword in your hands, you\'ll be inspired during your speeches to your companions in arms."};
descriptions["24681"]={cn:"这把剑什么都不怕，谁也不怕；它是如此无所畏惧，以至于你对任何事情都毫不在乎。",en:"This sword fears nothing and no one; it is so fearless that you too won\'t give a tuppence about anything."};
descriptions["24682"]={cn:"With its two blades, this ax is twice as formidable, and twice as effective at cutting off heads.",en:"With its two blades, this ax is twice as formidable, and twice as effective at cutting off heads."};
