descriptions["24685"]={cn:"有了这个，你就能把那些自称是赢家的人赶下颁奖台。",en:"Armed with this, you\'ll be able to knock all those self-proclaimed winners off their podiums."};
descriptions["24686"]={cn:"这把铲子能以极快的速度挖出敌人的坟墓。",en:"This shovel will dig your enemies\' tombs at breakneck speed."};
descriptions["24687"]={cn:"这个盾牌很容易受到攻击，所以要在你面前稳稳地拿住它。",en:"This shield is really quite happy taking hits, so hold it solidly before you."};
