descriptions["24700"]={cn:"This sword was forged in a masterful way by a world-renowned dark smith.",en:"This sword was forged in a masterful way by a world-renowned dark smith."};
descriptions["24701"]={cn:"This dagger keeps a trace of everything you kill using it. That\'s quite a notch on your belt!",en:"This dagger keeps a trace of everything you kill using it. That\'s quite a notch on your belt!"};
descriptions["24702"]={cn:"This dagger keeps a trace of everything you kill using it. That\'s quite a notch on your belt!",en:"This dagger keeps a trace of everything you kill using it. That\'s quite a notch on your belt!"};
descriptions["24703"]={cn:"Your spirit will be at peace with this shield, which protects you from all forms of physical harm.",en:"Your spirit will be at peace with this shield, which protects you from all forms of physical harm."};
descriptions["24704"]={cn:"Your spirit will be at peace with this shield, which protects you from all forms of physical harm.",en:"Your spirit will be at peace with this shield, which protects you from all forms of physical harm."};
descriptions["24705"]={cn:"授予勇往无前之人的勋章。",en:"A medal to reward the bravest of the brave."};
descriptions["24706"]={cn:"这片破裂不堪的布片是从垂死敌人身上拿到的，虽然是件奇怪的战利品，但总比头皮好多了。",en:"This unrecognizable scrap of cloth was torn from your dying enemy. You keep strange trophies, but it\'s still better than a scalp collection."};
descriptions["24707"]={cn:"This dagger keeps a trace of everything you kill using it. That\'s quite a notch on your belt!",en:"This dagger keeps a trace of everything you kill using it. That\'s quite a notch on your belt!"};
descriptions["24708"]={cn:"从腐烂尸体上取得的塔土。",en:"This Earth-Earth comes from a poorly-preserved corpse."};
descriptions["24709"]={cn:"似乎会动的塔泥，微妙的东西。",en:"Towpeat that seems to move, the tricky thing."};
descriptions["24710"]={cn:"在这塔晶中能看到微小的班点。",en:"You can see tiny flecks of Towermaline in this Aventowerine."};
descriptions["24711"]={cn:"这副首饰有时会颤动得非常厉害。",en:"This amulet quakes very strongly at times."};
descriptions["24712"]={cn:"一旦戴上这戒指，它就卡死了。",en:"Once your your put it on your finger, it\'s stuck there."};
descriptions["24713"]={cn:"这件结实的披风能从人世的疯狂中保护你。",en:"This solid cape will protect you from man\'s madness."};
descriptions["24714"]={cn:"由翻松的土壤制成，适合庄稼。",en:"This helmet was made from loose soil, suitable for crops."};
descriptions["24715"]={cn:"外表不值一提，但能轻易挡掉任何刀刃。",en:"They aren\'t much to look at, but these Crusts will easily deflect any blade."};
descriptions["24716"]={cn:"穿这双靴子时，把脚踏稳。",en:"You can wear these boots, but keep your feet on the ground."};
descriptions["24717"]={cn:"这条腰带耗时八天才完成，挺耗时间的...以腰带来说。",en:"This belt formed over the course of eighty days, which is quite long... for a belt."};
descriptions["24718"]={cn:"正确使用时能将人转化为行尸...或直接杀了他。",en:"When used correctly, this pike can turn a person into the living-dead... or just kill them outright."};
descriptions["24719"]={cn:"把队友的尸体用作盾牌很恶心，那用敌人的如何？",en:"It\'s nasty to use your allies\' bodies as shields, but what about those of your enemies?"};
descriptions["24720"]={cn:"将他们全数埋葬的武器。",en:"A sword with which to bury them all."};
descriptions["24721"]={cn:"这件超重的披风，能保护世界免受你的黑暗面危害。",en:"This extremely heavy cape will protect the world from your dark presence."};
descriptions["24722"]={cn:"闻起来不错，就像新翻的泥土。",en:"This emblem smells good, like freshly dug earth."};
descriptions["24723"]={cn:"伴随着配戴者直至死亡彼端。",en:"This emblem will accompany its wearer to death and beyond."};
descriptions["24724"]={cn:"一根强大的魔杖，属于有史以来最伟大的死灵术士。",en:"A powerful wand that belonged to one of the greatest necromancers the world has ever seen."};
descriptions["24725"]={cn:"一位时间法师的妹妹在被奴隶贩子绑走之前，会在她晚上的表演戴着这东西，哪种类型的就不说了。",en:"The sister of a Xelor who was kidnapped by slave drivers used to wear this thing for her nightly shows, the nature of which I will not repeat here."};
descriptions["24726"]={cn:"打开包裹，看看里面的礼物吧！",en:"Open this pouch and behold the gift within!"};
descriptions["24727"]={cn:"如果你感到寂寞，这件肩甲能陪伴着你，只要你喜欢尸体的话。",en:"If you feel lonely, these epaulettes will keep you company, so long as you\'re fond of corpses."};
descriptions["24728"]={cn:"矿尸化使得这件服装有了些脉动。",en:"Their Veriun Dead transformation gave these clothes a bit of a beating."};
descriptions["24729"]={cn:"一把能准确分出四等分的剑，在某些配方上很有用...",en:"A sword that cuts very precisely into quarters. Quite handy for certain recipes..."};
descriptions["24730"]={cn:"这副首饰令此水晶那不凡的魅力更加闪亮动人。",en:"An amulet that makes the raw beauty of this great crystal shine through."};
descriptions["24731"]={cn:"这把剑会持续成长到变成巨大的尺寸为止。",en:"This sword grew until it reached a tremendous size."};
descriptions["24732"]={cn:"这件胸甲内在非常美丽，尤其是穿着的时候。",en:"This breastplate has much inner beauty, especially while being worn."};
descriptions["24733"]={cn:"这双靴子穿起来像踩在碎玻璃上，但不得不说真的很漂亮！",en:"These boots will give you the impression of walking on broken glass, but they are indeed beautiful!"};
descriptions["24734"]={cn:"九月之神曾经穿戴过的一副黯淡胸甲，充斥着死亡之力。",en:"A somber breastplate once worn by the Protector of Septangel. It is saturated with the power of the dead."};
descriptions["24735"]={cn:"可以给你心爱的人戴上，但毫无浪漫之处。",en:"This ring may be worn on your sweetheart\'s finger, but there\'s nothing romantic about it."};
descriptions["24736"]={cn:"由最美丽的玛瑙所装饰的高级配件。",en:"This belt is decorated with the most beautiful Agates, making it a high-class accessory."};
descriptions["24737"]={cn:"这根双头法杖是众所周知的上帝之杖的改良版本，是由爱之祭司在上帝之杖经过了诸多测试后所制造。这一件甚至是由她本人所使用过的，使其更为独特。",en:"This two-headed staff is an improved version of the well-known God Rod.  It was made after much testing with the God Rod by the Priestesses of Love. This model has even been used, which kind of makes it a unique item."};
