descriptions["24789"]={cn:"收集 100 块碎片，合成爆谷头盔。",en:"Collect 100 of these fragments to create a Cornpop."};
descriptions["24790"]={cn:"永远不放弃爆谷！永远...",en:"Never give up the Cornpop! Ever..."};
descriptions["24791"]={cn:"“我们要爆谷！”百万名饥饿的阿玛克纳人呐喊着，对于可能产生的剧变一无所知。",en:"\"Give us the Cornpop!\" exclaimed millions of hungry Amaknians, knowing nothing of the cataclysm that would follow."};
descriptions["24792"]={cn:"他们歌颂着这件披风的绚丽，在战场上无论敌我都对其感到惧怕，但却没人记得身着披风的人是谁。",en:"They sing songs of this cape\'s splendor, the very same cape that terrified friend and foe alike on the battlefield. Yet no one remembers who wore it."};
