descriptions["24824"]={cn:"一根强大的魔杖，属于有史以来最伟大的死灵术士。",en:"A powerful wand that belonged to one of the greatest necromancers the world has ever seen."};
descriptions["24825"]={cn:"一位时间法师的妹妹在被奴隶贩子绑走之前，会在她晚上的表演戴着这东西，哪种类型的就不说了。",en:"The sister of a Xelor who was kidnapped by slave drivers used to wear this thing for her nightly shows, the nature of which I will not repeat here."};
descriptions["24826"]={cn:"如果你感到寂寞，这件肩甲能陪伴着你，只要你喜欢尸体的话。",en:"If you feel lonely, these epaulettes will keep you company, so long as you\'re fond of corpses."};
