descriptions["24830"]={cn:"一把能准确分出四等分的剑，在某些配方上很有用...",en:"A sword that cuts very precisely into quarters. Quite handy for certain recipes..."};
descriptions["24831"]={cn:"这副首饰令此水晶那不凡的魅力更加闪亮动人。",en:"An amulet that makes the raw beauty of this great crystal shine through."};
descriptions["24832"]={cn:"这把剑会持续成长到变成巨大的尺寸为止。",en:"This sword grew until it reached a tremendous size."};
descriptions["24833"]={cn:"这件胸甲内在非常美丽，尤其是穿着的时候。",en:"This breastplate has much inner beauty, especially while being worn."};
descriptions["24834"]={cn:"九月之神曾经穿戴过的一副黯淡胸甲，充斥着死亡之力。",en:"A somber breastplate once worn by the Protector of Septangel. It is saturated with the power of the dead."};
descriptions["24835"]={cn:"这根双头法杖是众所周知的上帝之杖的改良版本，是由爱之祭司在上帝之杖经过了诸多测试后所制造。这一件甚至是由她本人所使用过的，使其更为独特。",en:"This two-headed staff is an improved version of the well-known God Rod.  It was made after much testing with the God Rod by the Priestesses of Love. This model has even been used, which kind of makes it a unique item."};
descriptions["24836"]={cn:"这张卷轴允许你转变为中立（不属于任何国家）。你可以选择维持中立，或前往阿斯图布的国家公告板选择新的国籍！注意：使用后会失去所有功勋及荣誉奖章。",en:"Using this scroll will allow you to once more become Neutral (not affiliated with any Nation). You can then choose to remain Neutral, or to go to the Nation Board in Astrub to choose a new Nation! Warning: If you use this scroll, you will lose all you Merit Points and Glory Orbs."};
descriptions["24837"]={cn:"This Tofu was the poster boy for a great music group called the Dead Dennekies, before he kicked the bucket, thus dying.",en:"This Tofu was the poster boy for a great music group called the Dead Dennekies, before he kicked the bucket, thus dying."};
