descriptions["25071"]={cn:"拉亚·比恩善于交际，乐于邀请朋友们参加化妆舞会。他经常在派对上派发珠宝，以感谢宾客光临。",en:"Raya Bean made friends easily and often invited them to costume parties. He used to give the guests jewelry as party favors to thank them for attending."};
descriptions["25072"]={cn:"路七法有着双重人格。他是个勇猛的战士，同时他也是个无可救药的浪漫主义者...这在关键时刻会要了他的命！",en:"Lucy Fur is known to have two sides to her personality. Lucy Fur is known to have two sides to her personality. On the one hand, she is a fearsome warrior, on the other, she\'s a hopeless romantic... which could lead to critical situations!"};
