descriptions["25235"]={cn:"处於生死的夹缝之间，你不确定自己到底是生是死，就连死亡本身也无法确定。",en:"Between incarnation and excarnation, you no longer know if you\'re alive or dead. Death doesn\'t know either."};
descriptions["25236"]={cn:"化身为凶暴的正义。",en:"You embody a more violent form of justice."};
descriptions["25237"]={cn:"恐惧黑暗的烈焰吧...恐惧你最深的噩梦吧！",en:"Fear the fire of darkness... Fear your worst nightmare!"};
descriptions["25238"]={cn:"不幸的是，看来龙猪把你满嘴的牙齿都打飞了。",en:"Unfortunately, it seems the Dragon Pig knocked out all your teeth during your last encounter."};
descriptions["25239"]={cn:"你带来的灾难比黑鸦骑士或钢喙还严重。",en:"Your arrival portends even more dire calamities than the Black Crow or Steel Beak."};
descriptions["25240"]={cn:"「你以为可以给我溜走？」的正确答案。",en:"You came up with the right answer to the question \"Did you think you could give me the slip?\""};
descriptions["25241"]={cn:"人们总会说「诺戈？没人比牠强了！」之前可能如此，但现在可不是了。",en:"People always used to say \"Nogord? No one\'s stronger!\" It may have been true once, but not anymore."};
descriptions["25242"]={cn:"This sturdy and tenacious Haven Bag could also be used as a blunt weapon in a pinch.",en:"This sturdy and tenacious Haven Bag could also be used as a blunt weapon in a pinch."};
descriptions["25243"]={cn:"This extremely robust Haven Bag resists the elements well, but it\'s lined with Gobball wool for a very cozy interior.",en:"This extremely robust Haven Bag resists the elements well, but it\'s lined with Gobball wool for a very cozy interior."};
descriptions["25244"]={cn:"Is it really just a single Haven Bag, or are there several of them hiding behind that mask?",en:"Is it really just a single Haven Bag, or are there several of them hiding behind that mask?"};
descriptions["25245"]={cn:"肩膀上戴着甲吾和甲汝两兄弟。它们谁会先出手呢？两个都不会，它们都很烂。",en:"Pinchmie and Pinchyu are on your shoulders. Which one will strike first? Probably neither; they both kind of suck."};
descriptions["25246"]={cn:"浸湿的时候比较漂亮...相信我，没错的。",en:"This belt would look better down where it\'s wetter... take it from me."};
descriptions["25247"]={cn:"杀手的匕首。拥有它们的人可以挑战最凶恶的敌人。",en:"Bashers are fearful assassin\'s daggers. Whoever owns them will be able to rival even the most bloodthirsty warriors."};
