descriptions["25275"]={cn:"尖锐的小东西被恶魔依附着，它不放弃任何机会，攻击一切事物。我是你的话，情愿把它插在针扎上。",en:"This sharp little thing definitely has demons to lay to rest, as it pricks anything it can at the slightest opportunity. I\'d keep it stuck in a pin cushion if I were you."};
