descriptions["25282"]={cn:"自从有个和尚躲进螃蟹壳之后，他就潜心采集螃蟹腮毛，编织成了这顶腥臭的头盔。",en:"After leaving has-been boy band Hansum, Yke the Cwab Slayer set up shop selling malodorous helmets."};
descriptions["25283"]={cn:"我有个朋友曾经有一根这样的腰带。她喜欢嚼蟹肉棒，然后对我指手画脚。我们再也不是朋友了。",en:"My friend used to have one of these. He was constantly chewing on pieces of Cwab Stick and breathing down my neck. We\'re not friends any more."};
