descriptions["25401"]={cn:"你费了吃奶的力气才把这戒指从那只该死的鸵鸟腿上弄下来。于是你自豪地戴着它，时刻铭记不要脸的毅力才是王道。",en:"You went through hell and high water to wrestle this ring off that blasted Strich. Wear it proudly and never forget that perseverance is the key."};
descriptions["25402"]={cn:"你费了吃奶的力气才把这戒指从那只该死的鸵鸟腿上弄下来。于是你自豪地戴着它，时刻铭记不要脸的毅力才是王道。",en:"You went through hell and high water to wrestle this ring off that blasted Strich. Wear it proudly and never forget that perseverance is the key."};
descriptions["25403"]={cn:"为什么你最讨厌被别人挑刺，同时一旦有机会却最起劲地挑别人的刺？",en:"Why is it that you hate being criticized by others, but the moment you get the chance, you\'re the most critical of the lot?"};
descriptions["25404"]={cn:"This ax can cut anything from a Blibli to a Treechnid in half in one fell swoop, which, you have to admit, is not something you see every day.",en:"This ax can cut anything from a Blibli to a Treechnid in half in one fell swoop, which, you have to admit, is not something you see every day."};
descriptions["25405"]={cn:"This ax can cut anything from a Blibli to a Treechnid in half in one fell swoop, which, you have to admit, is not something you see every day.",en:"This ax can cut anything from a Blibli to a Treechnid in half in one fell swoop, which, you have to admit, is not something you see every day."};
descriptions["25406"]={cn:"泰坦巨人们经常举行庆典来膜拜他们的国王。这就是他们当时戴的皇冠。",en:"The titans used to hold festivals in Javian to worship their kings. This is the kind of hat they wore."};
descriptions["25407"]={cn:"泰坦巨人们经常举行庆典来膜拜他们的国王。这就是他们当时戴的皇冠。",en:"The titans used to hold festivals in Javian to worship their kings. This is the kind of hat they wore."};
descriptions["25408"]={cn:"不仅让你的腋下潮湿，还散发出一股兽...哦等等，那是你身上的气味...",en:"These epaulettes will not only make your armpits sweat, but also give off a beautiful scent of BO... Oh wait, that\'s you..."};
descriptions["25409"]={cn:"不仅让你的腋下潮湿，还散发出一股兽...哦等等，那是你身上的气味...",en:"These epaulettes will not only make your armpits sweat, but also give off a beautiful scent of BO... Oh wait, that\'s you..."};
descriptions["25410"]={cn:"漂亮极了...对鸵鸟来说是不是太高贵了？",en:"What a dandy neckpiece... Isn\'t it a bit too grand for a Strich?"};
descriptions["25411"]={cn:"鸵鸟归来！",en:"The Strich is back!"};
descriptions["25412"]={cn:"那些小混混再也不会麻烦你了！要讹钱，想都别想！送你几根羽毛回家插头发去！",en:"Those bullies won\'t bother you now! After years without a hair on your chest, now you have a proud, feathery chest wig!"};
descriptions["25413"]={cn:"An ax studded with sharp little teeth that can rip right through pretty much anything you care to try it out on.",en:"An ax studded with sharp little teeth that can rip right through pretty much anything you care to try it out on."};
descriptions["25414"]={cn:"不论你是汉子还是妹子，老鼠还是老虎，你都应当自豪地戴着这顶沙皇后冠...算了还是藏在包里吧...",en:"Whether you\'re man or mouse, woman or wolf, you should wear this Tsarina on your head proudly... or maybe just hide it in your bag..."};
descriptions["25415"]={cn:"冒险者布鲁斯特以其...恩...令人难忘的气味闻名于世。",en:"Blust the adventurer is best known for... well... his unforgettable odor."};
descriptions["25416"]={cn:"根据苹朵的形状雕刻而成。它们并不是从树上掉下来的，你知道的...",en:"This ring has been carved out of an Api. They don\'t grow on trees, you know..."};
descriptions["25417"]={cn:"让你精神饱满，这是它唯一的优点。天知道穿着它的人是怎样才忍住瘙痒的。",en:"This mass of Blibli fur makes its wearer more vigorous, which is important since no one knows how they manage to bear the tickling that long."};
