descriptions["25450"]={cn:"这件头饰的前端是用来反射阳光照瞎敌人眼睛的，所以夏天真的很管用，冬天么...不说了。",en:"Sunlight reflects off the front of this tiara to blind enemies and leave them helpless. Works like a charm in the summer, but winter\'s another story."};
