descriptions["25452"]={cn:"稳固支撑起你的躯干，没有任何缝隙。",en:"This breastplate encases your torso more firmly, because it\'s nowhere near as wobbly."};
descriptions["25453"]={cn:"纯粹由皇家咕哩碎片制成，闻起来像过期的干火腿。",en:"Made entirely out of scraps of Royal Blibli, this humdinger of an amulet stinks of dried-up ham that\'s waaaay past its smell-by date."};
descriptions["25454"]={cn:"戒指充满皇家力量。佩戴起来你会受到家养咕哩的膜拜。",en:"This ring has a regal strength about it. When you wear it, you will be respected by all the domesticated Bliblis."};
descriptions["25455"]={cn:"制造法杖其实很简单！找几块木头和几根线，随便缠一下，看！",en:"Who said creating weapons was complicated? Grab a few bits of wood, some string, and hey presto!"};
descriptions["25456"]={cn:"传说这把锤子会偷偷溜走。你最好时刻紧握着它。",en:"Legend has it that this mace has a tendency to wander. We would, therefore, advise you to keep it firmly attached to your fist at all times to make sure you don\'t lose it."};
descriptions["25457"]={cn:"不仅能用来招揽盟友，战斗中也很有用。",en:"Whip out this tough, sturdy bone to impress your allies. It\'s pretty useful in combat too."};
descriptions["25458"]={cn:"由尸体上的残骸制成。现在你知道为什么这套卡牌很容易弯曲了吧。",en:"These cards are made from the remains of corpses, which makes them particularly supple."};
descriptions["25459"]={cn:"两个脑袋总好过一个...前提是脑袋里还有东西。",en:"Two craniums are better than one... As long as they\'ve got something in them."};
