descriptions["26263"]={cn:"这把双刃剑使用的金属与伟大的黑鸦骑士之剑一样，这把剑更轻而且可以用单手挥舞。",en:"This double-bladed sword was forged from the same metal as the great Black Crow\'s Sword. It is lighter and can be wielded with one hand."};
