descriptions["26265"]={cn:"具有火焰的力量。",en:"This wand possesses the power of fire and flames."};
descriptions["26266"]={cn:"只要稍微超重...就会被这把剑切分。",en:"This sword\'ll carve up any opponent... Provided they\'re a few pounds overweight."};
descriptions["26267"]={cn:"永远不要信任它！",en:"This sword is not to be trusted!"};
descriptions["26268"]={cn:"这颗石头蕴含着月的邪恶部分。",en:"This stone contains Moon\'s evil essence."};
descriptions["26269"]={cn:"没有比这顶桂冠更好的奖励了。",en:"There\'s no finer reward than these Laurels."};
descriptions["26270"]={cn:"拿到金苹朵了！美味又高贵的金苹朵！你该拿给萨弗基亚的佣兵公会...还是拿给你的布丁朋友呢？",en:"I\'ve got a golden api! Appetizing, and very valuable! Should you take it to the Guild of Mercenaries in Sufokia... or give it to your Puddly friend?"};
descriptions["26272"]={cn:"授予在 976 年的沃土勇士中脱颖而出，伟大勇士的称号。",en:"This title is reserved for the great warriors who proved their worth among the Wakfu Warriors in the year 976."};
descriptions["26273"]={cn:"授予冠中之冠的称号。你已完全精通了猜拳，甚至不用手都可以猜拳。",en:"A title reserved for the champion of champions. You\'ve mastered rock-paper-scissors so completely, you can play it without even using your hands."};
descriptions["26274"]={cn:"哟吼吼，草莓味的。常年不洗，绅士最爱！",en:"These Ecaflipette panties have been carefully washed in \"Purrsil\" washing powder."};
descriptions["26275"]={cn:"This title is reserved for the valiant beta testers who pulled off a hold-up in the Stasis Dungeons.",en:"This title is reserved for the valiant beta testers who pulled off a hold-up in the Stasis Dungeons."};
descriptions["26276"]={cn:"给予你“超音速佣兵”的称号。使命必达，永远使命必达...",en:"This document allows you to use the title of \"Supersonic Mercenary\". The objective, always the objective..."};
descriptions["26277"]={cn:"给予你“布丁之友”的称号。你违背佣兵的使命而帮助了布丁们。",en:"This document allows you use the title \"Puddlies\' Friend\". You aided the Puddlies in violation of your prime objective as a mercenary."};
descriptions["26278"]={cn:"这件时装散发出的邪力，会连魔族都误以为你是他们的主人。",en:"The infernal power released by this costume is such that even Shushus could mistake you for their master."};
descriptions["26279"]={cn:"解放你的动物和灵魂本性，这件时装似乎能让你更加灵巧，并能够察觉到你周围的幽灵。",en:"Freeing both your animal and spiritual nature, this costume seems to make you much more cunning and allows you to discern the spirits around you."};
descriptions["26280"]={cn:"多亏了这件时装，你能够对应任何状况。然而，有件事得说，你脑中可能不再会只有你一人了。",en:"Thanks to this costume, you can face any situation. There is, however, a chance you won\'t quite be all alone in your head any more..."};
descriptions["26281"]={cn:"这件时装里有一只特别强大的魔族，而你现在是他的守护者了。小心不要变成了他的猎物...",en:"This costume contains an especially powerful Shushu; you are now its guardian, so be careful not to fall prey to it..."};
descriptions["26282"]={cn:"使用后会启动或关闭终结技。此物品不可堆叠。发动时会从启动的终结技里随机发动一个。",en:"Using this will activate or deactivate the Finisher. The item is not consumed. Random selection among all active Finishers."};
descriptions["26283"]={cn:"使用后会启动或关闭终结技。此物品不可堆叠。发动时会从启动的终结技里随机发动一个。",en:"Using this will activate or deactivate the Finisher. The item is not consumed. Random selection among all active Finishers."};
descriptions["26284"]={cn:"绝望、破灭、生气...这只残暴的魔族需要你的帮忙才有办法摧毁些什么东西。",en:"Despair, death, a bad mood... This Shushu of carnage will need your help if it wants to destroy anything whatsoever."};
descriptions["26285"]={cn:"历尽艰险的你赢得的奖励。你可以用这枚奖章兑换装备。",en:"You can trade in this hard-won token for pieces of equipment."};
descriptions["26286"]={cn:"噬影之牙的一片暗影。",en:"A piece of Shadofang\'s Shadow."};
descriptions["26287"]={cn:"最适合用来打理一头浓密长发的匕首，没有之一。幸运的是，它也适合用作不少其它用途。",en:"This is the best dagger for maintaining a long mane, bar none. Luckily, it\'s good for plenty of other things as well."};
descriptions["26288"]={cn:"可以把它戴在额头上，并束紧避免头太大。",en:"You can wear this around your forehead and tighten it to keep from getting a big head."};
descriptions["26289"]={cn:"穿上这副肩甲，在角落站直，然后微笑。你现在是支衣帽架了",en:"Put on these epaulettes, stand perfectly still in a corner, and then smile. You are now a coat rack."};
descriptions["26290"]={cn:"如果整个夏天在海边都穿着这件胸甲，你会有一身奇怪的肤色，但能免于晒伤。",en:"If you spend all summer at the beach wearing this chest armor, you\'ll get a weird-looking tan but will have avoided sunburn."};
descriptions["26291"]={cn:"这件披风让穿戴者的洗发精消耗量变为三倍。",en:"This cape triples its wearer\'s shampoo consumption."};
descriptions["26292"]={cn:"别惹毛这顶头盔，否则它会抓狂。",en:"Don\'t make this helmet mad, or it\'ll have a cow."};
descriptions["26293"]={cn:"过劳工作时可以穿这双靴子。",en:"You can wear this pair of boots when working yourself to death."};
descriptions["26294"]={cn:"这会是件最火热的新品饰件，只要它不会吸食穿戴者灵魂的话。",en:"This would be the hottest new accessory if it didn\'t suck up the wearer\'s soul."};
descriptions["26295"]={cn:"噬影之牙的发簪。",en:"This hairpin originally belonged to Shadofang."};
descriptions["26296"]={cn:"正如肉贩所说：“把肉摆在阴凉处才不会发臭。”这也适用于你其它部位。",en:"As butchers say, \"Keep meat in the shade to keep it from smelling bad.\" This could apply to other parts of your anatomy as well."};
descriptions["26297"]={cn:"据说噬影之牙就是用种戒指窃取目标的影子。",en:"They say this is the kind of ring Shadofang uses to steal her victims\' shadows."};
descriptions["26298"]={cn:"穿着这双靴子时别逗留在阴影下，否则影子会被夺走。",en:"Don\'t linger in the shadows with these boots, or they might just nab yours."};
descriptions["26299"]={cn:"拦路强盗 Mack Jessrine 最不喜欢的胸甲，总是说：“活在阴影里的人，永远也无法接近太阳。”",en:"The least favorite breastplate of the highwayman Mack Jessrine, who liked to say: \"If you live in the shadows, you\'ll never get close to the sun.\""};
descriptions["26300"]={cn:"即使这把铲子不间断的笑声令人烦躁，仍然是旅途中的好伙伴。",en:"As irritating as its constant laughter is, this shovel is nevertheless a great traveling companion."};
descriptions["26301"]={cn:"这枚附魔的戒指（我们不会说是受诅咒的，以免吓跑潜在客户）每当指向东边时就会发出咯咯笑声。用来指引方向非常有用。",en:"This enchanted ring (we won\'t call it cursed to avoid scaring off potential buyers) starts giggling when pointed east. Very useful for navigation."};
descriptions["26302"]={cn:"无论你心情多糟，这件披风都会向你露出笑容。",en:"No matter how hairy your mood, this cloak will always have a smile for you."};
descriptions["26303"]={cn:"戴上后会让你不断戏弄别人到再也停不下来为止，那时候你可能已经穿了一身约束衣了。",en:"Wearing this makes you kid around till you can\'t stop, at which point you might be wearing a straitjacket."};
descriptions["26304"]={cn:"警告：穿上这对肩甲可能会导致发狂，它们会无情地轮流戏弄你。",en:"Warning: These shoulder pieces could lead to insanity, as they\'ll take turns teasing you relentlessly."};
descriptions["26305"]={cn:"携带方便、安装简单，以备任何不时之需。无论是踏上冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。\n打开它只需要两秒！",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for setting off on an adventure or a picnic with your mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in just 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["26306"]={cn:"这个武器大师配方，让你学会制作“笑语铲”。",en:"This blueprint will teach you the recipe for the \"Laughing Shovel\" item for the Weapons Master profession."};
descriptions["26307"]={cn:"这个裁缝配方，让你学会制作“欢闹披风”。",en:"This blueprint will teach you the recipe for the item \"Hairlarious Cloak\" for the Tailor profession."};
descriptions["26308"]={cn:"最适合用来打理一头浓密长发的匕首，没有之一。幸运的是，它也适合用作不少其它用途。",en:"This is the best dagger for maintaining a long mane, bar none. Luckily, it\'s good for plenty of other things as well."};
descriptions["26309"]={cn:"可以把它戴在额头上，并束紧避免头太大。",en:"You can wear this around your forehead and tighten it to keep from getting a big head."};
descriptions["26310"]={cn:"穿上这副肩甲，在角落站直，然后微笑。你现在是支衣帽架了",en:"Put on these epaulettes, stand perfectly still in a corner, and then smile. You are now a coat rack."};
descriptions["26311"]={cn:"如果整个夏天在海边都穿着这件胸甲，你会有一身奇怪的肤色，但能免于晒伤。",en:"If you spend all summer at the beach wearing this chest armor, you\'ll get a weird-looking tan but will have avoided sunburn."};
descriptions["26312"]={cn:"这件披风让穿戴者的洗发精消耗量变为三倍。",en:"This cape triples its wearer\'s shampoo consumption."};
descriptions["26313"]={cn:"别惹毛这顶头盔，否则它会抓狂。",en:"Don\'t make this helmet mad, or it\'ll have a cow."};
descriptions["26314"]={cn:"过劳工作时可以穿这双靴子。",en:"You can wear this pair of boots when working yourself to death."};
descriptions["26315"]={cn:"这会是件最火热的新品饰件，只要它不会吸食穿戴者灵魂的话。",en:"This would be the hottest new accessory if it didn\'t suck up the wearer\'s soul."};
