descriptions["26318"]={cn:"拦路强盗 Mack Jessrine 最不喜欢的胸甲，总是说：“活在阴影里的人，永远也无法接近太阳。”",en:"The least favorite breastplate of the highwayman Mack Jessrine, who liked to say: \"If you live in the shadows, you\'ll never get close to the sun.\""};
descriptions["26319"]={cn:"即使这把铲子不间断的笑声令人烦躁，仍然是旅途中的好伙伴。",en:"As irritating as its constant laughter is, this shovel is nevertheless a great traveling companion."};
descriptions["26320"]={cn:"美丽记忆，永久珍藏。",en:"A nice trophy for your personal collection."};
descriptions["26321"]={cn:"这枚附魔的戒指（我们不会说是受诅咒的，以免吓跑潜在客户）每当指向东边时就会发出咯咯笑声。用来指引方向非常有用。",en:"This enchanted ring (we won\'t call it cursed to avoid scaring off potential buyers) starts giggling when pointed east. Very useful for navigation."};
descriptions["26322"]={cn:"无论你心情多糟，这件披风都会向你露出笑容。",en:"No matter how hairy your mood, this cloak will always have a smile for you."};
descriptions["26323"]={cn:"戴上后会让你不断戏弄别人到再也停不下来为止，那时候你可能已经穿了一身约束衣了。",en:"Wearing this makes you kid around till you can\'t stop, at which point you might be wearing a straitjacket."};
descriptions["26324"]={cn:"警告：穿上这对肩甲可能会导致发狂，它们会无情地轮流戏弄你。",en:"Warning: These shoulder pieces could lead to insanity, as they\'ll take turns teasing you relentlessly."};
descriptions["26325"]={cn:"穿着这件时装时，你觉得自己总是领先对手一步。欢迎踏入八奇的思考领域...",en:"While wearing this costume, you feel you\'re always a step ahead of your opponents. You know it knows that you know..."};
descriptions["26326"]={cn:"This costume puts you in the shoes of the first Masqueraider. Let\'s hope it doesn\'t make you want to destroy the World of Twelve in turn.",en:"This costume puts you in the shoes of the first Masqueraider. Let\'s hope it doesn\'t make you want to destroy the World of Twelve in turn."};
descriptions["26327"]={cn:"This mimilk is the best you\'ll ever drink.",en:"This mimilk is the best you\'ll ever drink."};
descriptions["26328"]={cn:"This mimilk is particularly good and the taste stays with you longer.",en:"This mimilk is particularly good and the taste stays with you longer."};
descriptions["26329"]={cn:"克洛夫撞上你时掉落的铃铛，得找个铁匠修复。",en:"This bell came off when you were thrashed by Cloovrr. It needs to be repaired by a blacksmith."};
descriptions["26330"]={cn:"巴坎德赋予了这铃铛新生命，你现在能将它物归原主了。",en:"Mournful Sniff has given this bell new life. You can return it to its owner."};
descriptions["26331"]={cn:"Although it looks harmless, this sample shows the plant is growing abnormally.",en:"Although it looks harmless, this sample shows the plant is growing abnormally."};
descriptions["26332"]={cn:"这件装饰能将你的坐骑与低阶魔族融合，能装备在龙鸟或军鸟上。",en:"This harness can fuse your mount with Minor Shushus; can be used to equip a Dragoturkey or Dragosteed."};
descriptions["26333"]={cn:"用回收装备制造的物品，用来制作强力的史诗和遗物符文。",en:"This item made of recycled equipment is used in the fabrication of extremely powerful epic and relic runes."};
descriptions["26334"]={cn:"打开包裹，看看里面的礼物吧！",en:"Open this pouch and behold the gift within!"};
descriptions["26335"]={cn:"You\'ve collected the substance in a flask. It gives off an atrocious odor. Hurry and take it to Shika Ingalsse.",en:"You\'ve collected the substance in a flask. It gives off an atrocious odor. Hurry and take it to Shika Ingalsse."};
descriptions["26336"]={cn:"This wheat was in contact with Stasis and grew abnormally large. There\'s a good chance it\'s not fit for consumption.",en:"This wheat was in contact with Stasis and grew abnormally large. There\'s a good chance it\'s not fit for consumption."};
descriptions["26337"]={cn:"All you have to do is say the name of an item in your bag out loud and this magical Haven Bag kit will find it for you. How handy!",en:"All you have to do is say the name of an item in your bag out loud and this magical Haven Bag kit will find it for you. How handy!"};
descriptions["26338"]={cn:"10 years ago, a legend began, but this time, it wasn\'t your own!",en:"10 years ago, a legend began, but this time, it wasn\'t your own!"};
descriptions["26339"]={cn:"The Shushu contained within this Haven Bag kit seems particularly insatiable, so watch your fingers!",en:"The Shushu contained within this Haven Bag kit seems particularly insatiable, so watch your fingers!"};
descriptions["26340"]={cn:"此庇护袋外观为你完成一个十二世界挑战后的奖励！",en:"This Haven Bag kit is your reward for completing a World of Twelve challenge!"};
descriptions["26341"]={cn:"你与噬影之牙决战后捡起了这条老旧的腰带。也许会有用处吧...",en:"You picked up this old useless belt after a showdown with Shadofang. Could be useful for something, though..."};
descriptions["26342"]={cn:"This ultra-violet dye emits a powerful Stasis energy.",en:"This ultra-violet dye emits a powerful Stasis energy."};
descriptions["26343"]={cn:"This Fanatic Fragment radiates powerful Stasis energy.",en:"This Fanatic Fragment radiates powerful Stasis energy."};
descriptions["26344"]={cn:"即使只是残留物，依然压抑地让人喘不过气来。这件特殊的物品散发着毁灭能量。",en:"This outgrowth was torn off quite slowly, to maximize torment. This particular one has been irradiated with Stasis."};
descriptions["26345"]={cn:"A super-powerful scroll that teaches you the common class spell, Mastery of Weapons.",en:"A super-powerful scroll that teaches you the common class spell, Mastery of Weapons."};
descriptions["26346"]={cn:"A super-powerful scroll that teaches the common class spell, Fluctuation.",en:"A super-powerful scroll that teaches the common class spell, Fluctuation."};
descriptions["26347"]={cn:"A super-powerful scroll that teaches the common class spell, Mass Charm.",en:"A super-powerful scroll that teaches the common class spell, Mass Charm."};
descriptions["26348"]={cn:"A super-powerful scroll that teaches the common class spell, Marrow Bone.",en:"A super-powerful scroll that teaches the common class spell, Marrow Bone."};
descriptions["26349"]={cn:"You shut away this little flame inside a vial to take it to Katrina. It pulsates steadily, as if it were breathing.",en:"You shut away this little flame inside a vial to take it to Katrina. It pulsates steadily, as if it were breathing."};
descriptions["26350"]={cn:"代表你在椰树林里为红方的软皮。",en:"A buff proving that you played Kokokobana on the red team."};
descriptions["26351"]={cn:"代表你在椰树林里为黄方的软皮。",en:"A buff proving that you played Kokokobana on the yellow team."};
descriptions["26352"]={cn:"Despair, death, a bad mood... Unleash the Shushu lurking inside you!",en:"Despair, death, a bad mood... Unleash the Shushu lurking inside you!"};
descriptions["26354"]={cn:"Thanks to this title, everyone will know that you\'re the one to call should any Yokai reappear.",en:"Thanks to this title, everyone will know that you\'re the one to call should any Yokai reappear."};
descriptions["26355"]={cn:"这团火能在黑暗中为你照亮前路。它会随着时间过去而熄灭，所以如果要长时待着的话记得多带一点。",en:"This flame will light your way in dark places. It goes out naturally over time, so remember to take several of them with you if you plan on staying there a long time."};
descriptions["26356"]={cn:"独特的徽章，戴起来之后化身光能法师。",en:"This emblem will strengthen your Huppermage slightly."};
descriptions["26357"]={cn:"独特的徽章，戴起来之后化身厄运狗。",en:"This emblem will strengthen your Ouginak slightly."};
descriptions["26358"]={cn:"这个护身符是复制品。它似乎被黑暗魔法改变了。",en:"This amulet is a copy of the original. It appears to have been altered by dark magic."};
descriptions["26359"]={cn:"You\'ll have to constantly resist the temptation to nibble your amulet...",en:"You\'ll have to constantly resist the temptation to nibble your amulet..."};
descriptions["26360"]={cn:"It must have taken quite a few souls to create this magnificent Haven Bag kit.",en:"It must have taken quite a few souls to create this magnificent Haven Bag kit."};
descriptions["26367"]={cn:"Unlock the title: \"Rhythm in Your Feet\"",en:"Unlock the title: \"Rhythm in Your Feet\""};
descriptions["26368"]={cn:"一把能打开辛索尔地窖的钥匙。谁知道一位前海盗会在里面藏了些什么呢？",en:"A rudimentary key that opens Synosore\'s Cellar. Who knows what a former pirate could have hidden there?"};
descriptions["26369"]={cn:"在辛索尔地窖里找到的方巾，应该能让你装扮成海盗贼...应该吧。",en:"This bandana was found in Synosore\'s cellar; it should let you pass as a Rogue pirate... I said \"should\"."};
descriptions["26370"]={cn:"跟辛索尔借来的方巾，能让你扮成海盗贼去阻止他们的计划。",en:"The bandana was borrowed from Synosore; it let you pass yourself off as a Rogue pirate and foil their plans."};
descriptions["26371"]={cn:"A souvenir from your victory at Amakna\'s Mooligrr Prize Festival.",en:"A souvenir from your victory at Amakna\'s Mooligrr Prize Festival."};
descriptions["26372"]={cn:"Document signed by Fafahoff, promising to pay the pirates a hefty sum.",en:"Document signed by Fafahoff, promising to pay the pirates a hefty sum."};
descriptions["26373"]={cn:"A considerable sum of kamas that you got from Fafahoff.",en:"A considerable sum of kamas that you got from Fafahoff."};
descriptions["26375"]={cn:"This enigmatic costume will make you look much more wise and benevolent. You will be regularly overcome by an irrepressible desire to meditate about the world and your place in the universe.",en:"This enigmatic costume will make you look much more wise and benevolent. You will be regularly overcome by an irrepressible desire to meditate about the world and your place in the universe."};
descriptions["26376"]={cn:"With this costume, you will be but one with the Quadramental Breeze and will feel the power of each element, as well as the delicate equilibrium that holds them together on our plane of existence.",en:"With this costume, you will be but one with the Quadramental Breeze and will feel the power of each element, as well as the delicate equilibrium that holds them together on our plane of existence."};
descriptions["26377"]={cn:"Kwismas will be upon us soon, so this costume makes you look like one of Father Kwismas\'s faithful reindeer. It\'s up to you whether you want to pull the sleigh with them or not.",en:"Kwismas will be upon us soon, so this costume makes you look like one of Father Kwismas\'s faithful reindeer. It\'s up to you whether you want to pull the sleigh with them or not."};
descriptions["26378"]={cn:"Nothing seems to slake your thirst for new challenges. This costume made with dragon scales is a testament to your incomparable talent for hunting monsters.",en:"Nothing seems to slake your thirst for new challenges. This costume made with dragon scales is a testament to your incomparable talent for hunting monsters."};
descriptions["26379"]={cn:"尽管奥古带来了庞大的灾难，但各国就像凤凰一样正从灰烬中重生。穿上这件华丽的服装，加入重生的行列。但注意不要烧伤自己！",en:"Like the Phoenix, the nations are reborn from their ashes despite the cataclysms caused by Ogrest. Be part of this renewal by wearing this flamboyant costume. But be careful not to burn yourself!"};
descriptions["26380"]={cn:"With this costume, you get all dressed for your better half... or to find it!",en:"With this costume, you get all dressed for your better half... or to find it!"};
descriptions["26381"]={cn:"Celebrate the new year with this costume that will shower you with light once night falls. Thus, you\'ll be able to take a stroll in the settlements of the World of Twelve.",en:"Celebrate the new year with this costume that will shower you with light once night falls. Thus, you\'ll be able to take a stroll in the settlements of the World of Twelve."};
descriptions["26382"]={cn:"This little dragon just out of the egg is already a bit temperamental! You\'ll have to resist petting it if you don\'t want your fingers scorched.",en:"This little dragon just out of the egg is already a bit temperamental! You\'ll have to resist petting it if you don\'t want your fingers scorched."};
descriptions["26383"]={cn:"This state-of-the-art technology made of hundreds of little color-changing jellies shows images you are very familiar with. Thanks for your loyalty!",en:"This state-of-the-art technology made of hundreds of little color-changing jellies shows images you know so very well. Thanks for your loyalty!"};
descriptions["26384"]={cn:"This haven bag kit will remind you of the long winter evenings of your childhood.",en:"This haven bag kit will remind you of the long winter evenings of your childhood."};
descriptions["26385"]={cn:"This haven bag kit is the perfect gift for your heart\'s desire... Unless you prefer to keep it for yourself!",en:"This haven bag kit is the perfect gift for your heart\'s desire... Unless you prefer to keep it for yourself!"};
descriptions["26386"]={cn:"A few kamas in a cauldron and there you go! This haven bag kit will transform you into a true Leprechaun.",en:"A few kamas in a cauldron and there you go! This haven bag kit will transform you into a true Leprechaun."};
descriptions["26387"]={cn:"此庇护袋外观为你完成一个十二世界挑战后的奖励！",en:"This haven bag kit is your reward for completing a World of Twelve challenge!"};
descriptions["26388"]={cn:"此庇护袋外观为你完成一个十二世界挑战后的奖励！",en:"This haven bag kit is your reward for completing a World of Twelve challenge!"};
descriptions["26389"]={cn:"使用后会启动或关闭终结技。此物品不可堆叠。发动时会从启动的终结技里随机发动一个。",en:"Using this will activate or deactivate the Finisher. The item is not consumed. Random selection among all active Finishers."};
descriptions["26390"]={cn:"使用后会启动或关闭终结技。此物品不可堆叠。发动时会从启动的终结技里随机发动一个。",en:"Using this will activate or deactivate the Finisher. The item is not consumed. Random selection among all active Finishers."};
descriptions["26391"]={cn:"Have you heard of Leprecoors, imps from the World of Twelve? Well, you\'ve found their mythical pot of gold! This one didn\'t have any gold in it, but it will still make a nifty helmet.",en:"Have you heard of Leprecoors, imps from the World of Twelve? Well, you\'ve found their mythical pot of gold! This one didn\'t have any gold in it, but it will still make a nifty helmet."};
descriptions["26392"]={cn:"According to Saint Ballotwine tradition, wearing this hat in front of someone lets them know, subtly, that you\'re crushing on them.",en:"According to Saint Ballotwine tradition, wearing this hat in front of someone lets them know, subtly, that you\'re crushing on them."};
descriptions["26393"]={cn:"This cape has an unfortunate tendency to rub up against your sweetheart; you\'ll need to keep it in check.",en:"This cape has an unfortunate tendency to rub up against your sweetheart; you\'ll need to keep it in check."};
descriptions["26394"]={cn:"与樱桃树近似的品种，只在春节期间出现。据说许愿后把护身符挂上树枝，愿望就会实现。",en:"A species akin to cherry trees, these trees only appear during Spring Has Sprung. It is said that if you make a wish and hang a talisman from its branches, it will come true."};
descriptions["26395"]={cn:"Mystical Sakura wood is prized for its rareness, how easily it can be worked, and its light pink color.",en:"Mystical Sakura wood is prized for its rareness, how easily it can be worked, and its light pink color."};
descriptions["26396"]={cn:"This beautiful cape might be made out of wood but it\'s still nearly as light as fabric.",en:"This beautiful cape might be made out of wood but it\'s still nearly as light as fabric."};
descriptions["26397"]={cn:"This Dora, made from mystic Sakura wood, has a constant supply of buds growing from its crown.",en:"This Dora, made from mystic Sakura wood, has a constant supply of buds growing from its crown."};
descriptions["26398"]={cn:"经过深入广泛的研究，发现哞哞原来是用脖子上的铃铛互相交谈的。也许这是唯一能让骑士明白的沟通方式。",en:"After extended research on the subject, it has been discovered that Moogrrs use these bells to talk to one another. M aybe this could finally be a method of communication Iops understand?"};
descriptions["26399"]={cn:"从现在开始，你多了个漂亮的背包。随便你往里面塞什么。",en:"From now on, this udder will make a very nice pocket. It\'s up to you to decide what you want to keep in it."};
descriptions["26400"]={cn:"让冒险者拥有强健的骨骼和身躯，虽然冒险者大都很短命。",en:"This Mimilk helps the adventurer build strong bones and a sturdy constitution, all the way up to the end of his short life."};
descriptions["26401"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few drops should suffice."};
descriptions["26402"]={cn:"据说有拒人于千里之外的作用。用便便来盖房子，你肯定不会有任何邻里纠纷的。",en:"This dung reportedly has incredible powers of isolation. Build your house with it, and you won\'t have any trouble with the neighbors."};
descriptions["26403"]={cn:"哞哞身上最好吃最柔嫩的肉...",en:"This cut was taken from the heart, the softest and tenderest part of the Moogrr..."};
descriptions["26404"]={cn:"可以当做耳环，让你看起来十分有型拉风。",en:"Worn as an earring, this Cwab Eye will make you look stylish and distinguished."};
descriptions["26405"]={cn:"在布拉克玛，信天翁羽毛生意利润丰厚。当地的居民用它来折磨邦塔国民...",en:"Albatrocious Feather trade is a big hit in Brakmar. Its inhabitants use it to torture Bontarians..."};
descriptions["26406"]={cn:"显然狼祭司曾经用这只蟹钳来整理幼狼的鬃毛。她有点笨手笨脚的，不是吗？",en:"Apparently the Boowolfine used this very pincer to trim her Miliboowolves\' manes. She didn\'t do a very good job of it, did she?"};
descriptions["26407"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few drops should suffice."};
descriptions["26408"]={cn:"往剑鞘里洒一点，什么剑都能塞得进去。",en:"Pour some of this into your sheath and you\'ll be able to stick any sword you like inside it."};
descriptions["26409"]={cn:"聚会佳品。蟹肉棒鲜艳的色彩令人食欲大增。",en:"Great for parties, this Cwab stick\'s vibrant color will really brighten up your buffet."};
descriptions["26410"]={cn:"厚实有弹性的树叶，用作雨衣的理想选择。",en:"This thick and rubbery leaves make ideal raincoats."};
descriptions["26411"]={cn:"椰精眼睛和椰子很容易搞混。即便是你吃椰子的时候，总有人觉得你是在吃眼球。",en:"It\'s easy to confuse these Kokoko eyes with Kokonuts. Don\'t think anyone will look the other way if you try to eat one, though."};
descriptions["26412"]={cn:"你的战利品是椰子味的胡须。",en:"A Kokonut-flavored beard that you picked up from one of your conquests."};
descriptions["26413"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few drops should suffice."};
descriptions["26414"]={cn:"椰子充满了神秘。唯一可以肯定的是，如果上面有三个洞，那肯定是用来塞手指的。",en:"The Kokonut is quite a mystery. The only thing we know for sure about it is that if it has three holes, they must be to put your fingers in it."};
descriptions["26415"]={cn:"椰汁的诱人气味，促使你忍不住想喝上几口。小心，会把你的牙齿粘在一起！",en:"The strong smell of Kokonut coming from this sap will probably make you want to put it in your mouth. Careful, though, as it\'ll most likely stick your teeth together!"};
descriptions["26416"]={cn:"粗糙的猪皮，使用前需要经过特殊处理。",en:"This rough skin will need special treatment if you want to use it in your creations."};
descriptions["26417"]={cn:"就连邦塔的武器店都不如这片牙龈的武装危险。",en:"Even Bonta\'s weapons store isn\'t as well equipped and dangerous as this gum line."};
descriptions["26418"]={cn:"如果獠牙看上去很好斗，这很容易理解，它们天生就这样。",en:"Don\'t be annoyed if this tusk acts all defensive. It\'s just in its nature."};
descriptions["26419"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few drops should suffice."};
descriptions["26420"]={cn:"谁能想得到有一天你也用得到猪鬃？",en:"Who would have thought that one day the fleece of a big hairy pig might interest you?"};
descriptions["26421"]={cn:"不仅仅是鼻孔，而是整个鼻腔。注意细节。",en:"This is not a nose, it\'s a snout. Note the subtle difference."};
descriptions["26422"]={cn:"滋滋没翅膀走不了多远，拍死它易如反掌。",en:"Moskitos can\'t get very far without their wings, which is even more reason for you to pluck them off."};
descriptions["26423"]={cn:"床单上发现了四条滋滋腿！昨晚发生了什么事情？",en:"Four Moskito Paws! Now there\'s something that will make a nice addition to your collection!"};
descriptions["26424"]={cn:"罕见的触角，一直散发着创生力量。",en:"This rare horn is still bursting with Wakfu."};
descriptions["26425"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few drops should suffice."};
descriptions["26426"]={cn:"上面并没有很多烂泥，但是看起来还是很恶心。",en:"There\'s not Mushd to it and it looks a bit Mushd but there we have it; a Mushd hand."};
descriptions["26427"]={cn:"一点带有唾液以及滋滋胃酸的血液...呃，真是可口！",en:"A bit of blood mixed with saliva and a touch of Moskito gastric acid...  umm, tasty!"};
descriptions["26428"]={cn:"你可以通过扭曲的外表以及惊人的硬度辨别出鸵鸟嘴。许多布拉克玛的小孩在换牙齿的时候咬鸵鸟嘴来镇静自己。",en:"You can recognize Strich Beaks by their twisted appearance and their astonishing resistance. Many Brakmarian babies were given these to use as pacifiers when their teeth were coming through."};
descriptions["26429"]={cn:"有人说哪怕是一只鸵鸟上的两条腿，要完全相像也是不可能的。",en:"Some claim it\'s impossible to find two Strich legs of exactly the same size, even if you take them from the same bird."};
descriptions["26430"]={cn:"在路上遇到一枚完好无损的巨蛋是不太常见的事情，你要是看见里面有小鸟正在往外啄可不要大惊小怪。",en:"Owning a Gigantegg in perfect condition is as rare as it is cumbersome. Don\'t be surprised if you feel little bird pecks coming from inside it."};
descriptions["26431"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few drops should suffice."};
descriptions["26432"]={cn:"可以制成羽毛笔，也可以插在帽子上。",en:"Some wonderful books have been written with quills made from Strich Feathers. You can also use it to decorate your hat."};
descriptions["26433"]={cn:"重辣调味，经过数天卤制之后，再煮个半天，终于可以吃了。",en:"Prepared with strong spices, marinated a few days in an overpowering sauce, and cooked for a great many hours, this Strich neck can just about pass for edible."};
descriptions["26434"]={cn:"挑剔的骸骨军，行军时总会弄丢一堆腿骨。",en:"If you happen to run into this Chafer, he might have a bone or two to pick with you!"};
descriptions["26435"]={cn:"看起来是骸骨破坏者的骨盆！任何过去尝试探究其起源的人...最后都变成了一堆香肠片。",en:"A Chafer pelvis! Well, it certainly looks like one. Anyone brave enough to check in the past has ended up... looking like a pile of sliced sausage."};
descriptions["26436"]={cn:"多多跪拜，你就明白这颗牙齿的用途了。",en:"Learn to love and respect this resource and its multiple uses will become apparent."};
descriptions["26437"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few drops should suffice."};
descriptions["26438"]={cn:"由腿骨粉末制成。经过长年累月的战斗洗礼，它们已经被磨成烂泥。",en:"This flour is made from old Chafer Bones which have been reduced to mush by years of fighting... and swords."};
descriptions["26439"]={cn:"好脆弱，一棍子就能敲断。",en:"Can be broken by sticks and stones."};
descriptions["26440"]={cn:"布拉克玛的家常饰物，象征着对于力量的崇拜。把它磨成粉末的话，也可以做成苦味粗薄饼。",en:"The Scara Horn is a symbol of veneration in many Brakmarian households. If you grind it down to powder you can also use it to make very bitter and gritty pancakes."};
descriptions["26441"]={cn:"独角仙死亡的时候，心脏也会迅速腐蚀。收集它们的心脏很难，所以格外珍贵。",en:"Generally speaking, Scara Hearts decompose instantly when they die, which makes collecting them a particularly difficult job."};
descriptions["26442"]={cn:"不仅仅是陈年老便。富含大量黄金，让你分不清究竟该收藏还是丢弃。",en:"This is not just any old dung. This dung contains copious amounts of gold, which makes you wonder whether you should like or lump it."};
descriptions["26443"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few drops should suffice."};
descriptions["26444"]={cn:"这些烧瓶中的东西很容易制作，它有点新鲜藏红花的味道，只要一滴就会让喝进它的人痛苦不堪。",en:"These flasks, which can be easily reproduced, smell of fresh saffron and instill strength and suffering in anyone who drinks them."};
descriptions["26445"]={cn:"甲虫壳的的作用大多数用来制作盾牌，盔甲，斧以及摇篮。",en:"Scarapaces are mostly used to make shields, armor, axes, and cradles."};
descriptions["26446"]={cn:"有一种古老的消遣游戏在土匪之间流传，就是闲着无聊做做针线活。",en:"The old Riktus pastime of \"spinning a yarn\" comes from the fact that they used to spend their free time making their clothes."};
descriptions["26447"]={cn:"在这件衣服之下，你将会看到一张鲜血淋淋的头皮，它是属于一个人的，毋庸置疑！",en:"Under the cloth, you\'ll find a nice, bloody piece of scalp. This used to belong to a head, no doubt about it!"};
descriptions["26448"]={cn:"很漂亮的缠腰布。也许短了一点，但是真的很漂亮。",en:"Drape yourself in this standard and you will have a very pretty loincloth. It might be a bit short, of course, but pretty all the same!"};
descriptions["26449"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few drops should suffice."};
descriptions["26450"]={cn:"几乎...是万恶之源。",en:"The essence of all evil... or almost!"};
descriptions["26451"]={cn:"This will really give you a sparkling grin!",en:"This will really give you a sparkling grin!"};
descriptions["26452"]={cn:"如果你实在不知道这些稻草的用处，那就用它来清理你的眼睛吧。",en:"If you can\'t find anything else to do with them, why not use these little bits of straw for cleaning out your ears."};
descriptions["26453"]={cn:"谁能缝一件漂亮的奴隶制服出来？谁能？",en:"Who\'s going to be able to make a magnificent slave suit? What? Who?"};
descriptions["26454"]={cn:"A moist, sludgy substance leaks out of it.",en:"A moist, sludgy substance leaks out of it."};
descriptions["26455"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few drops should suffice."};
descriptions["26456"]={cn:"只有牛头人能喝这种加倍刺激的苹朵汁而不至于把胃翻个底朝天。",en:"Only Taurs can drink this extra-strength api juice without turning their stomachs inside out."};
descriptions["26457"]={cn:"You wonder what the purpose of this bottle might very well be.",en:"You wonder what the purpose of this bottle might very well be."};
descriptions["26458"]={cn:"如果你没有脚蹼，可以试着用这些鱼鳍游泳。",en:"If you haven\'t got palms, start learning to swim using these fins instead."};
descriptions["26459"]={cn:"传说奥古曾经用来当牙签...你也可以试试。",en:"Legend has it that Ogrest used to use these Zordfish beaks as toothpicks... I dare you to do the same."};
descriptions["26460"]={cn:"即便被扯下来，仍然酷劲十足。",en:"Even all ripped up, this dorsal fin looks way cool."};
descriptions["26461"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few drops should suffice."};
descriptions["26462"]={cn:"炸虾的理想选择，100%无脂肪。等等，是100%脂肪。",en:"Ideal for frying Grawns in, this oil is 100% fat-free. Oh no wait, it\'s 100% fat."};
descriptions["26463"]={cn:"鱼肉是刺激味蕾的佳肴，让你尝到新鲜活力的海洋气息。",en:"Snapper Flesh is a delicacy for the taste buds. It will bring all the tastes of the tide to life for you."};
descriptions["26464"]={cn:"这棵树根是树精有脚气的良好佐证。",en:"This piece of wood is the foul-smelling irrefutable proof that Treechnids have foot-odor issues!"};
descriptions["26465"]={cn:"就算强如树精，依然要经受青春期的磨练...",en:"Even Treechnids must endure the inconvenience of puberty..."};
descriptions["26466"]={cn:"远古树精的最后残留...你手中握着的，是历史残片。",en:"This bark is one of the last existing pieces of the Ancestral Treechnid... You\'re holding a piece of history in your hands."};
descriptions["26467"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few drops should suffice."};
descriptions["26468"]={cn:"摩擦树精的树干几分钟后你就可以得到这种精华，它的作用主要是用来制备止咳糖浆。",en:"Rub the trunk of a Treechnid for a few minutes and you get this sap, mainly used in the preparation of throat syrup."};
descriptions["26469"]={cn:"从树灵脂化石中提炼而成。看起来像一个巨大的绵球血块。",en:"From fossilized Treechnid sap. Something like a large Gobball blood clot, in fact."};
descriptions["26470"]={cn:"一拍错音，希望没其它人注意到。",en:"A false note. Let\'s just hope no one else noticed it."};
descriptions["26471"]={cn:"You don\'t need to know how to play it to impress your guests.",en:"You don\'t need to know how to play it to impress your guests."};
descriptions["26472"]={cn:"Owning this essence won\'t make you any more of a maestro in difficult times.",en:"Owning this essence won\'t make you any more of a maestro in difficult times."};
descriptions["26473"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few drops should suffice."};
descriptions["26474"]={cn:"It\'s a sort of mucus left behind by Blops when they move around.",en:"It\'s a sort of mucus left behind by Blops when they move around."};
descriptions["26475"]={cn:"This flask contains a strange pink substance. And a multitude of melodies.",en:"This flask contains a strange pink substance. And a multitude of melodies."};
descriptions["26476"]={cn:"这个伐木工配方，让你学会制作“精装圣诞树”。",en:"This blueprint will teach you the recipe for the \"Monbow Tree\" item for the Lumberjack profession."};
descriptions["26477"]={cn:"刚剪掉了树枝，它马上就长了回来，真神奇！如果把几棵结合起来，也许会更大。",en:"Right after you cut it, it begins to grow back. It\'s truly magic! Maybe if you combine several, yours will be even bigger."};
descriptions["26478"]={cn:"There\'ll always be a little piece of Kwismas in your haven bag.",en:"There\'ll always be a little piece of Kwismas in your haven bag."};
descriptions["26479"]={cn:"This title is a reward for making the World of Twelve more beautiful with all these blossoming Sakuras.",en:"This title is a reward for making the World of Twelve more beautiful with all these blossoming Sakuras."};
descriptions["26480"]={cn:"With this title, you let everyone know that you too come from the lands of the Great North.",en:"With this title, you let everyone know that you too come from the lands of the Great North."};
descriptions["26481"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few drops should suffice."};
descriptions["26482"]={cn:"这件披风设计的用意就是让你穿上时不会隐形。",en:"No, no, you won\'t be invisible when you wear this cape. It\'s deliberate."};
descriptions["26483"]={cn:"这件披风设计的用意就是让你穿上时不会隐形。",en:"No, no, you won\'t be invisible when you wear this cape. It\'s deliberate."};
descriptions["26484"]={cn:"带着这只戒指时别照镜子。",en:"Don\'t look in the mirror while wearing this ring."};
descriptions["26485"]={cn:"带着这只戒指时别照镜子。",en:"Don\'t look in the mirror while wearing this ring."};
descriptions["26486"]={cn:"如果你需要帮助来赢得战斗，这条腰带每次都是赌注。",en:"If you need help winning fights, this belt is a winning bet every time."};
