descriptions["26494"]={cn:"这把剑是十二世界中最强大的宝物之一。必须与阿玛克纳戒指一同装备。",en:"This sword is one of the most formidable treasures in the World of Twelve. It cannot be carried without the Amakna Ring."};
descriptions["26495"]={cn:"这把剑是十二世界中最强大的宝物之一。必须与萨弗基亚戒指一同装备。",en:"This sword is one of the most formidable treasures in the World of Twelve. It cannot be carried without the Sufokia Ring."};
