descriptions["26497"]={cn:"这把剑是十二世界中最强大的宝物之一。必须与布拉克玛戒指一同装备。",en:"This sword is one of the most formidable treasures in the World of Twelve. It cannot be carried without the Brakmar Ring."};
descriptions["26498"]={cn:"不管怎么戴，看起来都会是歪向一边。",en:"No matter how you wear this hat, it will always look like it\'s on sideways."};
descriptions["26499"]={cn:"不管怎么戴，看起来都会是歪向一边。",en:"No matter how you wear this hat, it will always look like it\'s on sideways."};
descriptions["26500"]={cn:"这顶头饰不会让你更加令人生畏，也绝对不会更加强大...如果稍加思索，光是想到一些天真的灵魂会把你误认为古尔塔，你简直疯了。",en:"This headgear won\'t really make you any more fearsome, and definitely not more powerful... And if you think for a moment that some naive souls will mistake you for Goultard, well you\'re crazy."};
