descriptions["26502"]={cn:"非常适合摆在花园里，也可作为前门的地垫垫使用。",en:"Ideal for gardens, the Grazor can also be used as a welcome mat at your front door."};
descriptions["26503"]={cn:"非常适合摆在花园里，也可作为前门的地垫垫使用。",en:"Ideal for gardens, the Grazor can also be used as a welcome mat at your front door."};
descriptions["26504"]={cn:"这枚华美的戒指来自另一个星球。",en:"This magnificent ring comes from another planet."};
