descriptions["26506"]={cn:"这条护符原属于一位传奇的酷洛守护者，他是一位每天四处飞往帮助无助灵魂的猫头鹰。你一定很想送那位猫头鹰一只苍蝇。",en:"This amulet was worn by a legendary Protector of the Krosmoz, an owl who spent every day flying to the help of lost souls. We know, you\'d have loved to give that owl a fly."};
