descriptions["26673"]={cn:"你的小果冻在看了你的战斗之后进化了。现在是一种新的橙色，它看起来比以前更加自信和抗揍，通过同样的场合加强你的力量。",en:"Your Gemlin has evolved after watching you fight. Now a new orangish color, it seems much more confident and resistant than before, strengthening you by the same occasion."};
descriptions["26674"]={cn:"你的小果冻在看了你的战斗之后进化了。现在是一种新的紫色，它似乎能够帮助你集中你的治疗能力。",en:"Your Gemlin has evolved after watching you fight. Now a new purplish color, it seems able to help you focus your curative powers."};
descriptions["26675"]={cn:"你的小果冻在看了你的战斗之后进化了。现在是一种新的蓝色，它似乎拥有更高的视野，以帮助你更好地瞄准你的法术。",en:"Your Gemlin has evolved after watching you fight. Now a new bluish color, it seems to possess heightened vision to help you target your spells better."};
descriptions["26676"]={cn:"你的小果冻在看了你的战斗之后进化了。现在是一种新的红色，它似乎充满了根深蒂固的愤怒，助长了你自己的破坏力。",en:"Your Gemlin has evolved after watching you fight. Now a new reddish color, it seems full of deep-seated rage that fuels your own destructive power."};
descriptions["26677"]={cn:"你的小果冻在看了你的战斗之后进化了。现在是一种新的绿色，它特别关注它周围的环境，这样你就不会错过沿途的任何东西。",en:"Your Gemlin has evolved after watching you fight. Now a new greenish color, it pays particularly close attention to its surroundings so you won\'t miss anything along your path."};
