descriptions["26815"]={cn:"在过去用来惩罚年轻的潘达卢西亚人的时候，它被放在地上，傲慢的年轻人会被迫光着脚踮起脚尖站在上面几个小时，直到他们的眼泪流出来。不幸的是，这样好的传统正在消失，如今的年轻人忘记了如何遵循这个规则。",en:"Used in the olden days to punish young Pandissidents, it was placed on the ground and uppity young\'uns would be forced to stand on it barefoot and on tiptoes for hours until their tears were flowing. Unfortunately, such good traditions are being lost and young\'uns today are forgetting how to toe a straight line."};
