descriptions["27034"]={cn:"这双靴子曾经属于 Trey Panay 医生，一位专治头痛的前外科医生。",en:"These boots once belonged to Dr. Trey Panay, a former surgeon specializing in headache removal."};
descriptions["27036"]={cn:"什么东西的牙齿大、胡子和尾巴长？绝对不是玄武。",en:"What has big teeth, a mustache, and a long tail? Definitely not a black turtle."};
descriptions["27038"]={cn:"如果只能有一件，那一定是这件。",en:"If you absolutely had to keep only one pair, it would be this one."};
descriptions["27040"]={cn:"这条树干会把你的对手吓得半死，而你则牢牢地靠在自己的树干上。",en:"This trunk will drive your opponents off their rockers and keep you firmly on yours."};
descriptions["27041"]={cn:"有些生物需要不断地浇水（这里咳嗽两声）才能生长和开花。",en:"Some living beings need to be watered (cough with alcohol cough) constantly to grow and blossom."};
descriptions["27042"]={cn:"著名的植物学家Dar Kandire对这种奇怪的根茎进行了长期的研究。没有人知道他得出了什么结论。",en:"This strange root was long studied by the illustrious botanist, Dar Kandire. No one knows what conclusions he reached."};
descriptions["27043"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few drops should suffice."};
descriptions["27044"]={cn:"不要把它们放在一起，否则这些植物会开始跳一支振奋人心的康加舞。",en:"Don\'t put them next to each other or these plants could start dancing a rousing conga line."};
descriptions["27045"]={cn:"安放在双脚、膝盖或鼻子，但无论如何，不要忘记在旁边放一勺香草冰淇淋。",en:"Plant them with your feet, your knee or your nose, but whatever you do, don\'t forget a scoop of vanilla ice cream on the side."};
descriptions["27046"]={cn:"前面光滑，后面粗糙。这种皮肤会让人想起不好的回忆。",en:"Smooth in front, raspy behind. This skin brings back bad memories."};
descriptions["27047"]={cn:"半空还是半满？",en:"Is it half empty or half full?"};
descriptions["27048"]={cn:"你确定要打开它吗？",en:"Are you sure you want to open it?"};
descriptions["27049"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few grains should suffice."};
descriptions["27050"]={cn:"又刺鼻又臭。就像小屁孩一样。",en:"Irritating and smelly. Just like children."};
descriptions["27051"]={cn:"这只爪子在所有“惹恼史密斯的爪子”中排名前五。",en:"This claw is in the top 5 of all \"claws that annoy smiths\"."};
descriptions["27052"]={cn:"这张美妙的毛皮能让你保持温暖，还附送免费的跳蚤。",en:"This lovely fur will keep you warm and toasty. The fleas are just a free bonus."};
descriptions["27053"]={cn:"这张布匹浸满了雄性费洛蒙，能做出很棒的服装！",en:"Soaked through and through with the pheromones of an alpha male, this fabric makes wonderful clothes!"};
descriptions["27054"]={cn:"祸豹只使用这些图腾来猛击那些过于好奇的冒险家的头部。",en:"Blightopards only use these totems to bash overly curious adventurers over the head."};
descriptions["27055"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few drops should suffice."};
descriptions["27056"]={cn:"仅仅一小撮毛，却恶臭无比。",en:"It\'s just a tiny tuft of fur, but it\'s more than smelly enough already."};
descriptions["27057"]={cn:"这肉看起来很恶心，但是真的很可食用。",en:"This meat is disgusting to look at, but really quite edible."};
descriptions["27058"]={cn:"只有幽灵才能制造出这么奇怪的物质。好吧，也有可能是一只发情的绵团...",en:"Only Ghostofs can produce a substance as strange as this. Well, either them or Gobblettes in heat..."};
descriptions["27059"]={cn:"来自远古的尘埃，效力惊人。能让一切事物迅速衰老。很神奇吧！",en:"This powder might come from the Dofus Era, and its effects are surprising. It instantly ages anything it\'s mixed with. Magic, right?"};
descriptions["27060"]={cn:"如此沉重，你不禁好奇怎么有办法带着两颗在身上。",en:"It\'s so heavy you wonder how anyone could ever carry two at once."};
descriptions["27061"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few grains should suffice."};
descriptions["27062"]={cn:"这件旧布料太旧了，看起来很可疑...",en:"This piece of old fabric is so worn out that it seems very suspicious..."};
descriptions["27063"]={cn:"关于一件无比美丽事物的梦，但你仍在睁开眼的那一刹那全数遗忘。",en:"This dream was a thing of rare beauty, and yet you still forgot it the instant you opened your eyes."};
descriptions["27064"]={cn:"酷毙了！",en:"Cooool, man!"};
descriptions["27065"]={cn:"和你交谈的人都认为你和其他孩子一样是个 12 岁的孩子。但事实上，你不止如此，你是个被优化过的孩子！",en:"People you talk to think you\'re a Twelvian like the others. In reality, though, you\'re more than that. You\'re a Twelvian who\'s been optimized."};
descriptions["27066"]={cn:"这件胸甲来自于一位被奥古打倒的冒险家身上，它能展现你阴暗血腥的一面！",en:"Reassert your shadowy, bloody style with this breastplate from a fallen adventurer. Yes, fallen. He should never have gone after Ogrest!"};
descriptions["27067"]={cn:"在阿斯图布酒馆兑换 Boss Smasher 活动的奖励。",en:"This token will let you obtain the Boss Smasher event rewards.\nHead to Astrub Inn to trade in your tokens!"};
descriptions["27068"]={cn:"在阿斯图布地下室兑换你独特的徽章。",en:"Head to the Astrub cellars to trade this token for a lovely emblem of your very own."};
descriptions["27069"]={cn:"你为社区比赛设计了一套很棒的服装...用这个称号证明给大家看！",en:"You designed a fabulous costume for a community contest... And this title proves it for everyone to see!"};
descriptions["27070"]={cn:"在阿斯图布酒馆地下室的机器上兑换您的代币以获得丰厚奖励。",en:"Exchange your token for nice rewards at the machine in the basement of the Astrub Inn."};
descriptions["27071"]={cn:"用力吹邦塔单簧管，发出噪音。",en:"Try out the clarinet, an instrument with a sound as pure as the Bonta air!"};
descriptions["27072"]={cn:"用力吹阿玛克纳长笛，发出噪音。",en:"Try out the flute, an instrument with a sound as enchanting as the fields of Amakna!"};
descriptions["27073"]={cn:"用力打布拉克玛邦哥鼓，发出噪音。",en:"Try out the bongo, an instrument with a sound as agitated as Brakmar alleys!"};
descriptions["27074"]={cn:"用力吹萨弗基亚小号，发出噪音。",en:"Try out the trumpet, an instrument whose sound sticks with you like Sufokia starfish!"};
descriptions["27075"]={cn:"两千多年的竹文化正注视着你！",en:"Twenty centuries of bamboo culture are staring back at you!"};
descriptions["27076"]={cn:"这个械卡造型会让你看起来像奥古，只是没有那么强大！",en:"This Mecha skin will make you look like Ogrest, only much less powerful!"};
descriptions["27077"]={cn:"这个小家伙比看上去更强大。小心！许多脾气暴躁的冒险家为了给它一脚而弄断了脚趾...",en:"This little creature is more powerful than it looks. Watch out! Many a grumpy adventurer has broken a toe trying to give it a little kick..."};
descriptions["27078"]={cn:"收集 100 块碎片，合成骨感腰带。",en:"Collect 100 of these fragments to create a Chafeerce Belt."};
descriptions["27079"]={cn:"收集 100 块碎片，合成墨黑之纱。",en:"It takes 100 of these fragments to create an Inky Veil."};
descriptions["27080"]={cn:"收集 100 块碎片，合成穿孔靴。",en:"Collect 100 of these fragments to create a pair of pierced boots."};
descriptions["27081"]={cn:"收集 100 块碎片，合成挚爱肩甲。",en:"Collect 100 of these fragments to create Fave O\'Right Epaulettes."};
descriptions["27082"]={cn:"这件华美的服装是给予跨越许多挑战之人的奖励。",en:"A magnificent costume to reward a worthy individual who\'s faced many a challenge."};
descriptions["27083"]={cn:"用来将装备新增或提升附魔效果。",en:"These shards can be used to enchant equipment sockets to add or evolve effects."};
descriptions["27084"]={cn:"使用时可以让你切换跑步的方式，这个物品不会被消耗。",en:"When used, this item activates or deactivates a type of running. This item is not consumed."};
descriptions["27085"]={cn:"使用时可以让你切换跑步的方式，这个物品不会被消耗。",en:"When used, this item activates or deactivates a type of running. This item is not consumed."};
descriptions["27086"]={cn:"使用时可以让你切换跑步的方式，这个物品不会被消耗。",en:"When used, this item activates or deactivates a type of running. This item is not consumed."};
descriptions["27088"]={cn:"我的剑是我的真爱。类似的剑还有很多，但这一把是我的。",en:"My sword is my true love. There are lots of similar swords out there, but this one is mine."};
descriptions["27089"]={cn:"有了这个徽章，你会轻声说话，几乎是耳语。",en:"With this emblem, you\'ll speak softly, almost in a whisper."};
descriptions["27090"]={cn:"有了这个徽章，你会轻声说话，几乎是耳语。",en:"With this emblem, you\'ll speak softly, almost in a whisper."};
descriptions["27091"]={cn:"这个皮匠配方，让你学会制作“奥铎麦的朝圣鞋”。",en:"This blueprint will teach you the recipe for the item \"Otomai\'s Pilgrim Shoes\" for the Leather Dealer profession."};
descriptions["27092"]={cn:"这个制甲师配方，让你学会制作“奥铎麦门徒胸甲”。",en:"This blueprint will teach you the recipe for the item \"Otomai\'s Disciple Armor\" for the Armorer profession."};
descriptions["27093"]={cn:"谜语：我是由回收不需要的东西而来。我是？\na) 岳母/婆婆\nb) 彩虹粉末\nc) 对于岳母/婆婆的老套说法\nd) 以上皆是",en:"Riddle: I\'m made out of recycled waste. What am I?\na) A mother-in-law.\nb) Powder.\nc) A cliche about mother-in-laws.\nd) All of the above."};
