descriptions["27204"]={cn:"当你穿上这件服装后，日光消逝、最黑的夜晚突然降临。但别想着可以许愿！",en:"When you wear this costume, all daylight fades and the darkest night suddenly falls. No way you\'ll be granting wishes!"};
descriptions["27205"]={cn:"这只可爱的熊猫幼崽会跟随你到任何地方，用它又大又圆的眼睛探索世界的奥秘。",en:"This cute Pandawa cub will follow you everywhere, discovering the world\'s mysteries with its big round eyes."};
descriptions["27206"]={cn:"总有一天，它会变成一个卑鄙的魔族，无休止地折磨着十二世冒险家的灵魂。但现在，它只是一个可爱的，人畜无害的生物。",en:"One day it\'ll become a vile Shushu, endlessly tormenting the souls of adventurers from the World of Twelve. But for now, it\'s just an adorable, defenseless creature."};
descriptions["27207"]={cn:"它似乎认为你是它母亲。",en:"It seems to think you\'re its mother."};
descriptions["27208"]={cn:"Ratchams are often mistaken for rats, due to their tail, long ears, and lack of body hair. But if you adopt one, you\'ll soon find out how little this pawed predator has in common with a rodent. As cuddly as they come, it\'ll lick your face, and you\'ll discover that Ratchams are, in fact, not completely lacking in hair.",en:"Ratchams are often mistaken for rats, due to their tail, long ears, and lack of body hair. But if you adopt one, you\'ll soon find out how little this pawed predator has in common with a rodent. As cuddly as they come, it\'ll lick your face, and you\'ll discover that Ratchams are, in fact, not completely lacking in hair."};
