descriptions["27276"]={cn:"无论你身在何方，都能用吸管享用到美味的竹奶。",en:"Perfect for drinking bamboo milk with a straw everywhere you go."};
descriptions["27277"]={cn:"穿上它！然后华丽地粉碎你的对手！",en:"Gorgeous! Smashing! Fabulous!"};
descriptions["27278"]={cn:"有些人靠在你的肩膀上，却感觉靠在了鞋子上。",en:"Some of you have your head on your shoulders, others have boots."};
descriptions["27279"]={cn:"这双鞋子只有 12.5 码的。",en:"Only available in size twelve and a half."};
descriptions["27280"]={cn:"穿上它！然后华丽地粉碎你的对手！",en:"Gorgeous! Smashing! Fabulous!"};
descriptions["27281"]={cn:"虽然这枚戒指蕴含着巨大的力量，但持有者会因为一股奇怪的力量变得非常易怒。一定有办法能破除这个魔咒。",en:"Despite the power contained in this ring, its bearer remains bridled by a strange force. There must surely be a way to break the evil spell."};
descriptions["27283"]={cn:"这件来自过去的资源能用来启动 141 至 200 级地下城的石碑：\n恶之源、械卡工厂、机械迷城、紫金城、椰人地下城、汉尼芭地下城、尼罗鳄地下城、汉尼草地下城、獾兽巢穴、熔岩火山、蛋龙庇护地、冰盖峰、祸豹峡谷、潘达拉坟墓。",en:"This resource from the past can be used to activate steles in several dungeons from levels 141 to 200:\nWellspring of Evil, Mecha Factory, Ow El Dungeon, Forbidden City, Tropickle Dungeon, Kanniball Dungeon, Crocodyl Dungeon, Kannivore Dungeon, Badgeroxes\' Lair, Or\'Hodruin Volcano, Dreggons\' Sanctuary, Iced-Over Crest, Blightopard Canyon, Pandala Tomb."};
descriptions["27284"]={cn:"这件来自过去或未来的资源——取决于你所在的时间，能用来制作枯竭头皮。",en:"This resource from the past - or perhaps the future, depending on when you are - can be used to make a Thirster scalp."};
descriptions["27285"]={cn:"顶上从此寸毛不生。",en:"Nothing can grow on your head now. Nothing."};
descriptions["27286"]={cn:"顶上从此寸毛不生。",en:"Nothing can grow on your head now. Nothing."};
descriptions["27287"]={cn:"你总算得到它了！这是一名叫做睿森的熊猫战士的传奇斧头。",en:"You\'ve finally found it! The legendary ax of an incredible Pandawa warrior who went by the name of Reason."};
descriptions["27288"]={cn:"你总算得到它了！这是一名叫做睿森的熊猫战士的传奇斧头。",en:"You\'ve finally found it! The legendary ax of an incredible Pandawa warrior who went by the name of Reason."};
descriptions["27289"]={cn:"快给它东西喝，越快越好，不然它会吸干你的体液。",en:"Give it something to drink, ASAP, before it starts sucking all the moisture out of your body."};
