descriptions["27308"]={cn:"This hood will hide your ugly face and light up your eyes. You could be a living night-light for babies.",en:"This hood will hide your ugly face and light up your eyes. You could be a living night-light for babies."};
descriptions["27309"]={cn:"Arrows show the way in and out.",en:"Arrows show the way in and out."};
descriptions["27310"]={cn:"Cra\'s disciples have chosen this domesticated species of Prespic to be their walking quivers.\nIf they ever get to expensive to feed, they can also be used as training targets.",en:"Cra\'s disciples have chosen this domesticated species of Prespic to be their walking quivers.\nIf they ever get to expensive to feed, they can also be used as training targets."};
descriptions["27311"]={cn:"Its long hands will tickle you at night, scratch you when you nap, and pinch you the rest of the time.",en:"Its long hands will tickle you at night, scratch you when you nap, and pinch you the rest of the time."};
descriptions["27312"]={cn:"Its unique shape lets it collect rainwater to effortlessly clean the inside of your haven bag.",en:"Its unique shape lets it collect rainwater to effortlessly clean the inside of your haven bag."};
descriptions["27313"]={cn:"Young adventurers will knock on your haven bag door in the hopes of obtaining sweets if they can scare you.\nIf you don\'t want to be bothered, you can hand out rusty old nails or old toothbrushes instead.",en:"Young adventurers will knock on your haven bag door in the hopes of obtaining sweets if they can scare you.\nIf you don\'t want to be bothered, you can hand out rusty old nails or old toothbrushes instead."};
descriptions["27314"]={cn:"There\'s no safety, so it can go off very easily.",en:"There\'s no safety, so it can go off very easily."};
descriptions["27315"]={cn:"Perfect for the enemies of the enemies of your enemies.",en:"Perfect for the enemies of the enemies of your enemies."};
