descriptions["27353"]={cn:"尽管你是大龄儿童，你也一定会很喜欢这枚戒指！",en:"This ring is sure to be a hit with oldest of all you children out there."};
descriptions["27354"]={cn:"如果你想穿上这个护肩，你就要摄入大量的铁元素！只有足够强壮的人才能比拟费雷德隆爵士的威武！",en:"If you want to wear these epaulettes, you\'ll need to have pumped a whole lot of iron. Only the biggest and beefiest can compare to Fredalon\'s incomparable awesomeness..."};
descriptions["27355"]={cn:"当人们还在吧台对面喊着他们的口号时，这种靴子很流行。如今，所有的酷孩子都穿着“老城踢”，坐在桌边打着碟...十二岁的世界真的变了。",en:"These boots were popular back when people were still shouting their orders across the bar at the old \"Eye or See\". Nowadays, all the cool kids wear \"Old Town Kicks\" and text the \"Disk/Orb\" servers from their tables... The World of Twelve has really changed."};
descriptions["27356"]={cn:"Hogmeiser 用这些靴子去追逐他唯一真正不能忍受的生物：孩子。 对他们来说幸运的是，靴子太重了，他没法踢他们的屁股。",en:"Hogmeiser used these boots to chase after the only living creatures he truly couldn\'t stand: children. Luckily for them, the boots were too heavy for him to kick them in the butt."};
descriptions["27357"]={cn:"经验总结：不要愚蠢到在同一个人身上犯两次同样的错误！",en:"Experience is mainly a matter of not making the same dumb mistake twice."};
descriptions["27358"]={cn:"他们说那个工人把这件斗篷和魔界怪物的屁股皮缝在一起。如果那个工人真的知道怎么缝，这个故事也许有意义。",en:"They say that the Bworker sewed this cape together out of the skin from Rushu\'s rear end. That story might make sense if the Bworker actually knew how to sew."};
descriptions["27359"]={cn:"Positively crackling with static electricity. Handle with care!",en:"Positively crackling with static electricity. Handle with care!"};
descriptions["27360"]={cn:"Enough electricity to power an entire city... Too bad nobody uses electricity these days.",en:"Enough electricity to power an entire city... Too bad nobody uses electricity these days."};
descriptions["27361"]={cn:"Looking for a long, flexible tail? Look no further! And it\'s fashionable, too! Stiff, unmanageable tails are so 970.",en:"Looking for a long, flexible tail? Look no further! And it\'s fashionable, too! Stiff, unmanageable tails are so 970."};
descriptions["27362"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few drops should suffice."};
descriptions["27363"]={cn:"由于周遭有着静电的缘故，这些毛发永远都是竖着的。",en:"Thanks to the static electricity pouring out of it, these hairs are permanently standing on end."};
descriptions["27364"]={cn:"美味多汁的佳肴。麦麦·图推荐搭配带有蜘蛛腿的巧克力锅食用。",en:"A succulent, savory delight. E.Z. Yeast recommends sampling it in a chocolate fondue with Arachnee legs."};
descriptions["27365"]={cn:"拿起鸮鸟爪时要小心...它锐利得令人吃惊。也许是受到了不小的损伤，但还是能造成不小的伤害。",en:"Be careful when picking up the Bubourg claw... it\'s surprisingly sharp. It may be badly damaged, but it can still do plenty of damage itself."};
descriptions["27366"]={cn:"一小件机械零件，来自海尔伯格伯爵装在鸮鸟身上的奇怪护甲。",en:"A small mechanical piece collected from the strange armor that Count Harebourg placed on the Bubourgs."};
descriptions["27367"]={cn:"你不知道为什么这个骄傲而又阴沉的鸮鸟首领，要把这颗小栗子藏在一个安全的地方。这是他过往的遗物吗？一种永不忘记对他来说重要的事情的方法？你将它握在手中，誓言要无畏地踏上冒险之路。",en:"You don\'t know why the proud, somber leader of the Bubourgs was keeping this little chestnut tucked away in a safe place. Was it a symbol of his past? A way to always remember something important to him? You close your hand around it, vowing to forge bravely ahead with your adventure."};
descriptions["27368"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few drops should suffice."};
descriptions["27369"]={cn:"本质上来说这种羽毛是有机物，但它散发出某种更加黑暗的感觉。",en:"This feather is organic in nature, but it exudes a sense of something darker."};
descriptions["27370"]={cn:"这美味的鸮鸟肉让你欲罢不能！但要注意里面的小碎片。",en:"This delicious Bubourg meat will have you coming back for more! Just watch out for splinters."};
descriptions["27371"]={cn:"这个武器就是为什么剑不能参加高博球杯比赛的原因。它的拥有者，一个叫奈瓦尔的人，以 4 比 0 的比分赢得了每一场比赛，引起了观众的惊愕。",en:"This weapon is why swords are no longer allowed in Gobbowl competitions. Its owner, a certain E. Neval, won every one of his matches 4 to 0, causing much consternation among spectators."};
descriptions["27372"]={cn:"这个武器就是为什么剑不能参加高博球杯比赛的原因。它的拥有者，一个叫奈瓦尔的人，以 4 比 0 的比分赢得了每一场比赛，引起了观众的惊愕。",en:"This weapon is why swords are no longer allowed in Gobbowl competitions. Its owner, a certain E. Neval, won every one of his matches 4 to 0, causing much consternation among spectators."};
descriptions["27373"]={cn:"Kiotamm 总是大声评论对手的行动...然后利用他们的混乱，迅速削减他们的规模（字面上！）。当这种武器最终被禁止参加高博球杯比赛时，这位杰出球员的职业生涯悲剧性地结束了。",en:"Kiotamm always commented loudly on his opponents\' actions... then took advantage of their confusion to quickly cut them down to size (literally!). When this type of weapon was ultimately banned from Gobbowl competitions, this illustrious player\'s career was tragically cut short."};
descriptions["27374"]={cn:"Kiotamm 总是大声评论对手的行动...然后利用他们的混乱，迅速削减他们的规模（字面上！）。当这种武器最终被禁止参加高博球杯比赛时，这位杰出球员的职业生涯悲剧性地结束了。",en:"Kiotamm always commented loudly on his opponents\' actions... then took advantage of their confusion to quickly cut them down to size (literally!). When this type of weapon was ultimately banned from Gobbowl competitions, this illustrious player\'s career was tragically cut short."};
descriptions["27375"]={cn:"这种凉鞋有自动拦截功能，所以被禁止参加高博球杯比赛。穿着它的球员，达尔达·林，不停地攻击他的对手，直到他赢得所有比赛。在他的辩护中，他总是坚持说不是他，是他的凉鞋。",en:"These sandals feature an automatic tackling function, which is why they were banned from Gobbowl competitions. The player who wore them, Dulda Lin, kept tackling his opponents until he won all his matches by... \"forfeit\". In his defense, he always insisted that it wasn\'t him, it was his sandals."};
