descriptions["27377"]={cn:"这个武器就是为什么在高博球杯比赛中不允许打牌的原因。它们最初的主人，阿特安，是出了名的难以捉摸。以至于他几乎没有出现在赛场。",en:"This weapon is why cards are no longer allowed in Gobbowl competitions. Their original owner, Art\'And, was infamously elusive. So much so that he hardly ever appeared at the stadium."};
