descriptions["27422"]={cn:"把这张购物单戴在脖子上，以确保下次去商店时不会忘记任何东西。当你被邀请参加一个百味聚餐时，这仍然是避免带着蜘蛛毒和蜘蛛卵陷入困境的最好解释。",en:"Wear this shopping list around your neck to make sure you don\'t forget anything on your next run to the store. It\'s still the best way to avoid getting stuck bringing Strich eggs and Arachnee venom when you\'re invited to a Rat Clette potluck."};
