descriptions["27426"]={cn:"在萨弗基亚之外，戴这顶帽子可能会让你看起来有点太可笑，你很难被认真对待。另一方面，在水下，它会让你看起来像个捕食者。别误会：这可能是个人见解。",en:"Outside of Sufokia, wearing this hat is liable to make you look just a tad too ridiculous, and you\'ll struggle to be taken seriously. Under water, on the other hand, it\'ll make you look like a predator. But make no mistake: it\'s just a matter of perception."};
