descriptions["27435"]={cn:"据说没有任何活人见过海尔伯格伯爵的脸，即使是在迫使他隐居的冻结发生之前也是如此。那顶帽子下究竟藏着张怎么样的脸，而这些年来又有了什么奇特的变化呢？?",en:"It\'s said that nary a living soul has ever seen Count Harebourg\'s face, even before the deep freeze that forced him to live in seclusion. What could he be hiding beneath this hat, and what strange transformations may have ravaged his face over the years?"};
