descriptions["27539"]={cn:"很难说是这件服装对你来说太大了，还是你对这件服装来说太小了。",en:"It\'s hard to say whether this costume isn\'t your size or whether you\'re not big enough to wear it."};
descriptions["27540"]={cn:"世界末日时为了生存可能会不得已吃掉饲主。",en:"It may be forced to eat its owner to survive the end of the World of Twelve."};
descriptions["27541"]={cn:"这只针织绒毛娃娃最高可以用华氏 104 度的水清洗。",en:"This knitted wool dolly can be washed by hand up to 104 degrees."};
descriptions["27542"]={cn:"还好潘朵拉有写笔记！",en:"Luckily for you, Pandora took notes!"};
descriptions["27543"]={cn:"携带方便，无论是踏上危险的冒险征途还是与丈母娘共进野餐都可轻松胜任。\n打开它只需要两秒！",en:"Easy to carry, perfect for your next bold adventure or picnics with the mother-in-law.\nUnfolds in 2 seconds!"};
descriptions["27544"]={cn:"这本百科似乎是由一名真正的狼专家所著。",en:"This encyclopedia seems to be the work of a bona fide Boowolf expert."};
descriptions["27545"]={cn:"从一名萨迪达守卫骷髅身上找到的日志。有几页被狂狼咬过。",en:"A journal found on the skeleton of a Sadida Guard. Some of the pages have been chewed on by a Moowolf."};
descriptions["27549"]={cn:"它们闻起来像是烤栗子和热葡萄酒。",en:"It smells like roasted chestnuts and mulled wine."};
descriptions["27550"]={cn:"你原以为这件披风就是海尔伯格伯爵能浮空的秘密...但你错了。",en:"You thought this cape held the secret of Count Harebourg\'s levitation ability... You were wrong."};
descriptions["27551"]={cn:"这副肩甲使人产生恐惧及敬畏之情，就像它的前主人一样。",en:"These epaulettes inspire fear and respect. Much like their previous owner."};
descriptions["27552"]={cn:"穿透这件胸甲的攻击可能会被往 90 度转向，但由于这件胸甲坚不可摧，因此也无从证实。",en:"Attacks that pierce this breastplate may be deflected by 90 degrees. But since the breastplate is indestructible, that\'s not yet completely confirmed."};
descriptions["27553"]={cn:"在海尔伯格伯爵他的城堡、他的灵魂、他的岛屿、他的怪物之中，唯一没有冻僵的是他的双脚，这都多亏了这双靴子。",en:"Between his castle, his soul, his island, and his monsters, Count Harebourg\'s feet are the only thing not frozen solid, thanks to these boots."};
descriptions["27554"]={cn:"据说没有任何活人见过海尔伯格伯爵的脸，即使是在迫使他隐居的冻结发生之前也是如此。那顶帽子下究竟藏着张怎么样的脸，而这些年来又有了什么奇特的变化呢？?",en:"It\'s said that nary a living soul has ever seen Count Harebourg\'s face, even before the deep freeze that forced him to live in seclusion. What could he be hiding beneath this hat, and what strange transformations may have ravaged his face over the years?"};
descriptions["27555"]={cn:"伯爵利用这枚戒指来引导他过剩力量所产生的多余能量，一旦失去控制甚至能轻易将他自己毁灭。所幸的是，这对你来说不是问题。",en:"The Count uses this ring to redirect the surplus energy produced by his excessive power, which could easily destroy him if ever he lost control of it. Fortunately, that\'s not an issue for you."};
descriptions["27556"]={cn:"飞速地围绕着你的腰际打转，使你晕头转向。",en:"Goes around your waist so fast, it\'ll make your head spin."};
descriptions["27557"]={cn:"显然地，这可以用来开启海尔伯格伯爵城堡的一扇秘密活门。话又说回来，海尔伯格伯爵的城堡本身就是个秘密地点了...",en:"Apparently, this can reveal a secret trap door in Count Harebourg\'s chambers. Then again, Count Harebourg\'s chambers are already a secret location in their own right..."};
descriptions["27558"]={cn:"这把钥匙可以解锁鸮鸟工厂和沙鼠地下城的一个乱入石碑等级。",en:"This key can be used to unlock an Intervention Stele level in the Bubourg and Gerbean dungeons."};
