descriptions["27568"]={cn:"这个珠裁缝配方，让你学会制作“潜水盔”。",en:"This blueprint will teach you the recipe for the item \"Dorabyss\" for the Tailor profession."};
descriptions["27569"]={cn:"使用魔药来启动或解除光环。该魔药无法被消耗。",en:"Using this potion will activate or deactivate your aura. The potion is not consumed."};
descriptions["27570"]={cn:"很难说这会给你带来好运还是厄运。\n可以肯定的是，它会让你的庇护袋里到处都是毛。",en:"It\'s hard to say if this will bring you good luck or bad.\nAll that\'s certain is that it will leave fur all over your Haven Bag."};
descriptions["27572"]={cn:"想念那趟很棒的旅程吗？遇到可爱的幸运猫并在拉玛纳格沙滩上享受美食的时光？正好，这个庇护宝石会让你觉得自己正在萨弗基亚的沙滩上，而且没有鲨鱼！",en:"Missing that awesome trip you took? When you met that cute Ecaflip and collected chefish on La Mädrague Beach? Well, this haven-gem will make you feel like you\'re on a Sufokian beach, minus the sharks!"};
descriptions["27573"]={cn:"用美丽而坚硬的鹅卵石作为装饰。这会让你想起那整晚在寒冷的人行道上度过的夜晚，想着怎么会落到这步田地。",en:"Adorn your interior with charming and sturdy cobblestone. It\'ll remind you of all the nights you spent sleeping on the cold pavement wondering how you ended up there."};
descriptions["27574"]={cn:"这个庇护宝石要不是烹饪实验失败的结果，就是个难以言喻的设计品味。无论是哪种情况，你都可以将受害者的骨灰藏在火山土壤中，而不会遭受怀疑。",en:"This haven-gem is either the result of a failed culinary experiment or simply unspeakable taste in interior design. Whatever the case may be, you can hide the ashes of your victims in the volcanic soil without raising any suspicion."};
descriptions["27575"]={cn:"如果你正在寻找经典的瓷瓦，那就在这了。这块石头使用了可追溯至千年之前的技术切割。",en:"If you\'re looking for classy, classic tiling, then look no further. This stone was cut using techniques that date back thousands of years."};
descriptions["27576"]={cn:"战斗结束时经验增加 50%。\n持续 120 分钟（游戏时间）且不可叠加。",en:"This potion increases the experience gained at the end of a fight by 50%.\nIt lasts 120 minutes (playing time) and is not stackable."};
descriptions["27577"]={cn:"战斗结束时掉落率增加 50%。\n持续 120 分钟（游戏时间）且不可叠加。",en:"This potion increases the chances of getting loot at the end of a fight by 50%.\nIt lasts 120 minutes (playing time) and is not stackable."};
