descriptions["27685"]={cn:"每个人都有梦想，但哀伤的是无法保证会实现。话说回来，如果真的很在乎某件事，就必须把它做好。",en:"Everyone has a dream, but there\'s sadly no guarantee of it becoming reality. Then again, if you really care about something, you have to try to do it right."};
