descriptions["27687"]={cn:"小滴的粘液不断从这把匕首上滴下来。就算没杀死对手，也至少可以恶心他们。",en:"A small trickle of mucus is constantly dripping from this dagger. If you don\'t manage to kill your opponent, at least you can disgust them."};
descriptions["27688"]={cn:"现在你可以戴着铃铛攻击敌人了！",en:"Now you can attack your enemies with bells on!"};
descriptions["27689"]={cn:"也许有点小，却承载着神圣绵球的灵魂之力，这股力量多年前被喀努斯吸取了。舔一口，有股干草的味道。",en:"It may be small, but this ring contains a fragment of Gobbsage\'s essence, absorbed long ago by Excarnus. Pop it in your mouth. It tastes like angry, digested hay."};
descriptions["27690"]={cn:"使用别人的脚穿越炽热的岩浆实在是太惬意了，看看它们还有很多其他的方便...我是说便利，便利快捷。",en:"It\'s always easier to walk across lava with someone else\'s feet on. These have the added benefit of looking grood... I mean good. And great. Great and good."};
descriptions["27691"]={cn:"夏天的烈日仍然不够火辣，这件胸甲给你再添一把火。",en:"As if the summer sun wasn\'t enough, here\'s a breastplate that aspires to be a radiator."};
descriptions["27692"]={cn:"每走一小步，腰带上的小铃铛都会剧烈摇动，任何人都会察觉到你在偷偷接近。漂亮和惊喜二选一。",en:"The little bells that adorn this belt jingle so violently that they make it impossible to sneak up on anyone. Look, it was either style or surprise. You can\'t have both!"};
descriptions["27693"]={cn:"一个集齐轻柔，舒适，飘逸，厚实于一身的羽毛护肩，不正是你对敌中需要的重要装备吗！",en:"A soft, comfortable, floaty, three-ply, feathery neck-dress. Just what you need to wipe enemies out!"};
descriptions["27694"]={cn:"不要忘了放松一点头盔带...否则脱下来的时候就难了！",en:"Don\'t forget to unfasten the leather straps that hold this helmet to your head... It might be a bit difficult to take it off, otherwise!"};
descriptions["27695"]={cn:"这段薄纱能让覆盖着的恶灵隐身。很多人为了找到这件稀世珍宝而付出了本来就不怎么正常的理智。",en:"A transparent veil that allows Excarnates to become invisible. Many a man is pushing up daisies after trying too hard to obtain this precious item."};
descriptions["27696"]={cn:"这双靴子的设计耗费了大量的心血，因此工匠制作出来的成品也自然是杰作。非同寻常的规模和使用的材料使这双靴子独一无二。多么吸引人的话题！当你穿着这双靴子时，轻而易举就能与人打破隔阂。",en:"Designing these boots took an enormous amount of work, so naturally, their crafter made a masterpiece of them. Both their unusual proportions and the materials used make them unique. Such a fascinating topic! Breaking the ice with just about anyone is a breeze when you wear them."};
