descriptions["27747"]={cn:"哈根·达兹曾经是个极地碎石者。他吞下了太多塔罗迪姆矿石，变异成了可怕的怪物！",en:"Hagen Daz was a Polar Crackler like the others, until the day he swallowed so much Taroudium for breakfast that he mutated into a terrifying monster!"};
