descriptions["27749"]={cn:"保暖性能极好，即便面临暴风雪也无所谓畏惧。",en:"These shoulder pads are incredibly frost-resistant and are very useful when plunging headlong into a blizzard, as you do."};
descriptions["27750"]={cn:"这个胸甲看起来只有轻薄一片，但是它的抵抗力却超乎你的想像之外。",en:"This breastplate appears to have been cast in a single piece. It protects against the often violent discharges that arise from metalwork."};
descriptions["27751"]={cn:"曾经是吉狼狼的项圈...",en:"This amulet could be used as a belt by the YeCh\'Ti\'Wawa, which is no reason to use it to tie up weaklings."};
descriptions["27752"]={cn:"相当惹眼的靴子，当年引得雪封村民疯抢。",en:"These boots allowed Missiz Freezz to convert a great deal of Frigost\'s population, who had initially been reluctant to serve her."};
