descriptions["27789"]={cn:"让戴上的手指成为手指之王，并被其它手指猎杀。",en:"This ring will make its wearer the king of fingers, and the other fingers will hunt for it."};
descriptions["27790"]={cn:"让戴上的手指成为手指之王，并被其它手指猎杀。",en:"This ring will make its wearer the king of fingers, and the other fingers will hunt for it."};
descriptions["27791"]={cn:"让戴上的手指成为手指之王，并被其它手指猎杀。",en:"This ring will make its wearer the king of fingers, and the other fingers will hunt for it."};
descriptions["27792"]={cn:"要是你再轻一些，这双靴子就能自己飞走了。",en:"These boots could fly away of their own accord if you were a bit lighter."};
descriptions["27793"]={cn:"要是你再轻一些，这双靴子就能自己飞走了。",en:"These boots could fly away of their own accord if you were a bit lighter."};
descriptions["27794"]={cn:"这一定就是你梦想中的头盔了。伤心的是，旁人可能会觉得你看起来像头猪。",en:"This has to be your dream headgear. Sadly, others might think it makes you look like a pig."};
descriptions["27795"]={cn:"这一定就是你梦想中的头盔了。伤心的是，旁人可能会觉得你看起来像头猪。",en:"This has to be your dream headgear. Sadly, others might think it makes you look like a pig."};
descriptions["27796"]={cn:"人生所至，脚之所行。",en:"Where life takes you, your feet drag you."};
descriptions["27797"]={cn:"人生所至，脚之所行。",en:"Where life takes you, your feet drag you."};
descriptions["27798"]={cn:"人生所至，脚之所行。",en:"Where life takes you, your feet drag you."};
descriptions["27799"]={cn:"正不胜邪？哈！只要你还挥舞着这把指针，就不可能发生这种事。",en:"Evil conquering good? Ha! As long as you brandish this clock hand, there\'s simply no chance of that."};
descriptions["27800"]={cn:"正不胜邪？哈！只要你还挥舞着这把指针，就不可能发生这种事。",en:"Evil triumphing? Ha! As long as you brandish this clock hand, there\'s simply no chance of that."};
descriptions["27801"]={cn:"这把剑是唯一没有被冰冷现实打断的梦。",en:"This sword is the only dream that isn\'t cut short by a cold dose of reality."};
descriptions["27802"]={cn:"这把剑是唯一没有被冰冷现实打断的梦。",en:"This sword is the only dream that isn\'t cut short by a cold dose of reality."};
descriptions["27803"]={cn:"欧萨莫达神用过的锤子，实际上是把打桩用的小铁锤。",en:"Used by the god Osamodas himself. Well, actually, it was more of a little hammer like this, mainly used for planting stakes."};
descriptions["27804"]={cn:"不必害怕，这条腰带记不得以前的主人。",en:"Have no fear: This belt doesn\'t remember its old owner."};
descriptions["27805"]={cn:"戴上它的任何人都会变得疯狂易怒。",en:"Anyone who wears this ring will become crazy and aggressive."};
descriptions["27806"]={cn:"令人无法将目光移开这顶帽子。",en:"You won\'t be able to take your eyes off this hat."};
descriptions["27807"]={cn:"枕着这对崭新的肩甲上睡上一觉。",en:"You\'ll be able to sleep soundly on your newly padded shoulders!"};
descriptions["27808"]={cn:"穿上这件上衣后，你所说的一切都会变得有说服力，并让他人崇拜你。",en:"Put on this jacket and everything you say will be eloquent and achieve cult status."};
descriptions["27809"]={cn:"缓解眼疲劳。",en:"This amulet is a sight for sore eyes, especially your own."};
descriptions["27810"]={cn:"千里之行，始于足下。",en:"Exploring crypts is a real kick!"};
descriptions["27811"]={cn:"所以...它象征着刻薄、令人厌烦。还想穿吗?",en:"Sooo... this cloak is mean and troublesome. Wanna wear it?"};
descriptions["27812"]={cn:"范内博抬头望向阿玛克纳船长。他一生都在努力想要成为那样的英雄，但他连边都还摸不着。",en:"Fannebuoy looked up to Captain Amakna. He spent his whole life trying to become a hero like him, but he never did quite manage."};
descriptions["27813"]={cn:"你可以傻努力一辈子，但仍然会有比你更厉害的人。重要的是提升自己并实现目标。但是...你仍然不会是最顶尖的。",en:"You can work yourself silly all your life, but there\'ll still be someone who\'s better than you. What matters is improving yourself and achieving your goals regardless. But... you\'re still not the best."};
descriptions["27814"]={cn:"这副手套会让你觉得自己像个国王，虽然是沮丧的那种。",en:"These gloves will make you feel like a king. A bit of a damp one, though."};
descriptions["27815"]={cn:"迪翠克曾经是范内博的死敌，但在发现原来他实际上很善良，并弄清楚一切只是误会之后关系就变好了。",en:"Once the sworn enemy of Fanneboi, Dee Tractor was actually good at heart and turned nice again after figuring out that the whole thing was just a misunderstanding."};
descriptions["27816"]={cn:"你个子够小的话，它就足够大以阻挡窥探的视线。",en:"If you\'re small enough, it\'ll be big enough to keep you hidden from prying eyes."};
descriptions["27817"]={cn:"试着去了解人们的故事和行动。这个命令塑造了科瓦克的整个人格。他是一位杰出的旅行者，他不断地努力帮助遇到的可怜人。\n他的力量：与他遇到的每个新朋友一起成长和学习。\n他的弱点：阿玛克纳饮料。",en:"Try to understand people\'s stories and actions. That command shaped Kovak\'s entire personality. He was a distinguished traveler who constantly tried to help the poor souls he encountered.\nHis strength: growing and learning with each new person he met.\nHis weakness: the beverages of Amakna."};
descriptions["27818"]={cn:"过往的岁月使这一终极遗物覆满了蘑菇，但仍从未如此般耀眼。",en:"The years gone by have covered this ultimate relic in mushrooms, but still it never shined so brightly."};
descriptions["27819"]={cn:"这顶头盔的优点与其它卓斯头盔相同。无论是炙热的日晒还是头部的打击，它都能起到保护作用。通过限制视线的设计，还可以防止佩戴者意识到危险。简而言之，这是一顶完美的战士头盔。",en:"This helmet has the same advantages as other Zoth headgear. It\'ll protect you from the sun no matter how hot it is and from blows to the head. It also prevents the wearer from being aware of danger by limiting what they can see. In short, this is the perfect warrior headgear."};
descriptions["27820"]={cn:"不想要被附近的拾荒者都拿走的话，最好赶快找到买家。",en:"You\'re gonna have to find a buyer fast if you don\'t want every scavenger in the neighborhood coming to pilfer it."};
descriptions["27821"]={cn:"艳阳尾巴被切下来后会再长回来。\n小心别切到别的什么，那可不会长回来。",en:"Sunsloth tails grow back over time if they are cut off.\nJust be careful not to cut anything else off, because that won\'t grow back."};
descriptions["27822"]={cn:"既然尾踏蝎能用尾巴踏东西，那脚要用来做什么？",en:"If a Stompion can stomp on things with its tail, then what does it do with its feet?"};
descriptions["27823"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few drops should suffice."};
descriptions["27824"]={cn:"保护艳阳生物不被晒伤，但无法避免被你烧伤。",en:"This protects Sunsloths from sunburn, but not from any burns you might inflict."};
descriptions["27825"]={cn:"不用煮，阳光早已把它烤熟了。",en:"Don\'t bother cooking it: The sun already gave it enough of a beating."};
descriptions["27826"]={cn:"别把这钳子玩得太过头，它也会反过来对你这么做。",en:"Don\'t make too much fun of this pincer or it\'ll return the favor."};
descriptions["27827"]={cn:"长时间接触这钳子会让皮肤非常难受。",en:"Long exposure to this pincer can be very hard on the skin."};
descriptions["27828"]={cn:"坚硬到就算把整座泽尼特山放上去也不会裂。",en:"It\'s so strong you could balance Mount Zinit on it and it wouldn\'t break."};
descriptions["27829"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few drops should suffice."};
descriptions["27830"]={cn:"壳甲生物失去鳞片时，会迅速长出新的鳞片。这就是为什么它们这么难以击倒的原因。",en:"When a Crabstacean loses a scale, a new one quickly grows back. That\'s why it\'s so difficult to beat them."};
descriptions["27831"]={cn:"壳甲生物的肉鲜嫩而美味，令人惊讶的是还具有催情作用。你知道下次约会该煮什么了！",en:"Crabstacean meat is extremely tender and tasty, and surprisingly, it has aphrodisiac properties. You know what to cook for your next date!"};
descriptions["27832"]={cn:"你真的不该用这张有冷却效果的皮革做保暖衣物。话说回来，也许会让你看起来比较酷...",en:"You really shouldn\'t try to make warm clothes with this leather, which has cooling properties. Then again, it might make you looker cooler..."};
descriptions["27833"]={cn:"据说这爪子造成的伤口永远不会痊愈。",en:"It\'s said that the injuries this claw inflicts never heal."};
descriptions["27834"]={cn:"火红牛奇特法术的残留物，即使是天才发明家也难以运用。",en:"This is a remnant of the Buffacophant\'s strange kind of magic. Even a genius inventor would have a hard time using it."};
descriptions["27835"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few drops should suffice."};
descriptions["27836"]={cn:"真是粗糙的毛！",en:"Now that\'s some rough hair!"};
descriptions["27837"]={cn:"需要煮上好几小时才能充分解冻加热。",en:"It needs to be cooked for many hours to properly heat and defrost it."};
descriptions["27838"]={cn:"这张皮革真的很硬，颜色也很微妙。",en:"This leather is really tough and subtly colored."};
descriptions["27839"]={cn:"实际上没有那么坚硬。",en:"This wood isn\'t really that tough."};
descriptions["27840"]={cn:"注意别不小心坐上去！",en:"Be careful not to sit on them by accident!"};
descriptions["27841"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few drops should suffice."};
descriptions["27842"]={cn:"肯定棘手...",en:"These should make for a thorny reception..."};
descriptions["27843"]={cn:"必须熬上很长一段时间并加入大量的香料来掩盖它可怕的味道。",en:"You\'ll have to simmer it for a long time and add a lot of spices to obscure its hideous flavor."};
descriptions["27845"]={cn:"凡是栽进土地的，土地必有所回报。",en:"Everything you put into the ground, the ground gives back someday."};
descriptions["27846"]={cn:"坚硬到几乎不可能劈开。",en:"This wood is so tough that it\'s almost impossible to chop it."};
descriptions["27847"]={cn:"你会跳森巴吗？",en:"Can you dance the Caryoka?"};
descriptions["27848"]={cn:"只生长在非常、非常湿润土壤里的独特树木。",en:"These unique trees only grow in really, really wet soil."};
descriptions["27849"]={cn:"能做成美味的沙拉，也能作为坚固的制作材料。",en:"This seaweed is delicious in salads, but it is also recognized as a solid crafting material."};
descriptions["27850"]={cn:"并非由音符组成，而是数千种复杂成分的产物。懂了没，伊欧普脑袋？把手拿开！",en:"Instead of being made of musical notes, this wood is the product of thousands of complex formulae. Got it, Iop brain? Hands off!"};
descriptions["27851"]={cn:"只在寒冷地方生长。",en:"This seed only grows in cool places."};
descriptions["27852"]={cn:"淡雅温和的味道与突破天际的热量形成鲜明的对比。",en:"The neutral, almost-bland taste of this cranberry is in stark contrast to the sky-high calorie content."};
descriptions["27853"]={cn:"这颗总是燃烧着的果实，哪怕是一秒也难以握住。",en:"Since it\'s always on fire, you can\'t really hold it for more than a second."};
descriptions["27854"]={cn:"大部分生长于干旱地方。",en:"This seed mostly grows in arid conditions."};
descriptions["27855"]={cn:"汁液略带粘性、呈咸味，使其成为世界各地婆婆们的爱用配料。",en:"Hactuses contain a slightly sticky, salty juice, making them a highly esteemed ingredient for meals for mothers-in-law everywhere."};
descriptions["27856"]={cn:"摸过后请彻底把手洗干净。",en:"Please wash you hands thoroughly after handling a Catchoo."};
descriptions["27857"]={cn:"生长在温带环境。",en:"This seed grows in temperate environments."};
descriptions["27858"]={cn:"可爱的紫花。",en:"A lovely violet flower."};
descriptions["27859"]={cn:"最受爱花人喜爱的花朵。",en:"This is a favorite among florists."};
descriptions["27860"]={cn:"这美丽的花朵通常生长于寒冷地区。",en:"This pretty flower usually grows in cold regions."};
descriptions["27861"]={cn:"绝无仅有的冰洁。",en:"Its purity is matched only by its iciness."};
descriptions["27862"]={cn:"这朵罕见的雪花永远不会融化。",en:"This rare flowerflake will never melt."};
descriptions["27863"]={cn:"历经数个世纪的冰霜后呈现苍白的颜色。",en:"This ore turned pale after being frozen for many centuries."};
descriptions["27864"]={cn:"是寒冷的地区使矿石冰冷，亦或是冰冷的矿石使地区寒冷？",en:"Is this ore cold because it\'s in a cold area, or is the area cold because of this ore?"};
descriptions["27865"]={cn:"超凡脱俗的颜色。",en:"Its color looks otherworldly."};
descriptions["27866"]={cn:"不仅是石头，还非常雄辩。必须对其多方打磨。",en:"Not just a stone, this Zircon also speaks extremely eloquently. It must be polished in every sense of the word."};
descriptions["27867"]={cn:"和善的生物。",en:"A gentle creature."};
descriptions["27868"]={cn:"爱咕哝，但配沙拉依然不错。",en:"This nice little Grawn has a habit of mumbling, but it\'s still great in salads."};
descriptions["27869"]={cn:"桌上有牡蛎的派对一定会很棒！",en:"You can be sure the party will be great when there are oysters on the table!"};
descriptions["27870"]={cn:"“有什么新鲜的？”",en:"\"So, what\'s Newtral?\""};
descriptions["27871"]={cn:"这片木板能用来制作家具、护甲或武器。",en:"This plank is used to make furniture, armor, or weapons."};
descriptions["27872"]={cn:"这袋面粉用来制作好吃、热呼呼的面包。",en:"This flour is used to make good, warm bread."};
descriptions["27873"]={cn:"这条绳线能用来制作头盔、护符和戒指。",en:"This string is used to craft headgear and helmets, but also amulets and rings."};
descriptions["27874"]={cn:"这块钢能用来制作武器、护甲或装饰。",en:"This steel can be used to craft weapons, armor, or decorations."};
descriptions["27875"]={cn:"这片鱼片能让你制作美味的餐点。",en:"This Tiramisoup lets you make lovely little dishes."};
descriptions["27876"]={cn:"这份精华包含了怪物的灵魂，能把力量注入几乎所有类型的物品。",en:"This essence contains monsters\' souls, and can instill their power into almost all types of items."};
descriptions["27877"]={cn:"用来烹调美味食物的香料。",en:"This spice is used to make lovely little dishes."};
descriptions["27878"]={cn:"用来制作披风和头饰的纤维。",en:"This fiber is mainly used to craft capes and headgear."};
descriptions["27879"]={cn:"用来制作武器的手柄。",en:"This handle is mainly used to make weapons."};
descriptions["27880"]={cn:"用来制作靴子、皮带和包的皮革。",en:"This leather is mainly used to craft boots, belts, and bags."};
descriptions["27881"]={cn:"用来制作胸甲、肩甲以及盾牌。",en:"This plate is mainly used to make breastplates, epaulettes, and shields."};
descriptions["27882"]={cn:"用来制作戒指和护符的宝石。",en:"This gem is mainly used to craft rings and amulets."};
descriptions["27883"]={cn:"用来制作美味面包和炸食物的油。",en:"This oil is used to make good, rich bread, and to fry your ingredients to prepare dishes."};
descriptions["27884"]={cn:"用在木工上的脚架。",en:"This bracket is used in all types of woodwork."};
descriptions["27885"]={cn:"蕴含着在十二世界中无可比拟的力量。",en:"The power this orb contains is unmatched in the World of Twelve."};
descriptions["27886"]={cn:"胶水是用来组合物品的绝佳选择。你可以从 201 到 215 的地图挑战任务中取得。",en:"Souper-Glou is the ideal ingredient to assemble your items. You can get it as a reward for the level 201 to 215 Environmental Quests."};
descriptions["27887"]={cn:"可以变更 215 级以内装备的元素加成。",en:"Can be used on an item (at level 215 or less) with variable elementary stats to get different stats among those possible."};
descriptions["27888"]={cn:"可以在下列兑奖机使用此奖章兑换奖励：蛮兽、艳阳、壳甲、冻原。",en:"Use the following machines to exchange your tokens for fantastic rewards: Vandalophrenic, Sunsloth, Crabstacean, Tundrazor."};
descriptions["27889"]={cn:"不推荐给害怕淋湿的人。",en:"Not recommended for anyone afraid of getting wet."};
descriptions["27890"]={cn:"俗话说得好，每朵玫瑰都有刺，对吧？",en:"Every rose has its horns. That\'s how the saying goes, right?"};
descriptions["27891"]={cn:"保护你免受微生物的侵袭，也保护其他人免受你唾沫的侵袭。",en:"Protects you from microbes, and others from your spittle."};
descriptions["27892"]={cn:"使用后会启动或关闭终结技。此物品不可堆叠。发动时会从启动的终结技里随机发动一个。",en:"Using this will activate or deactivate the Finisher. The item is not consumed. Random selection among all active Finishers."};
descriptions["27893"]={cn:"使用后会启动或关闭终结技。此物品不可堆叠。发动时会从启动的终结技里随机发动一个。",en:"Using this will activate or deactivate the Finisher. The item is not consumed. Random selection among all active Finishers."};
descriptions["27894"]={cn:"使用后会启动或关闭终结技。此物品不可堆叠。发动时会从启动的终结技里随机发动一个。",en:"Using this will activate or deactivate the Finisher. The item is not consumed. Random selection among all active Finishers."};
descriptions["27895"]={cn:"不能当做弹药。\n除非你别无选择。",en:"Not to be used as a projectile.\nUnless you have no other way to defend yourself."};
descriptions["27896"]={cn:"很难说它是粘稠的、粘性的、粘缠的、黏糊糊的还是满是鼻涕的。\n词汇量大的人会用粘液来形容它。",en:"Hard to say whether it\'s viscous, sticky, clammy, slimy, or just snotty.\nThose with a large vocabulary would describe it as mucilaginous."};
descriptions["27897"]={cn:"这个傲慢的小毛球总是斜眼儿看你，甚至当你直视它的眼睛的时候。",en:"This arrogant little furball will always look at you sideways, even when you\'re looking it straight in the eyes."};
descriptions["27898"]={cn:"和这个小石怪保持一步之遥。",en:"Keep this little stone creature a stone\'s throw away."};
descriptions["27899"]={cn:"破宠物胜过没宠物。",en:"A bad pet is better than no pet."};
descriptions["27900"]={cn:"表达你的仇恨而不伤害你的仇家。",en:"Express your animosity without injuring the target of said animosity."};
descriptions["27901"]={cn:"总是从枕头大战开始...",en:"It always starts with a pillow fight..."};
descriptions["27902"]={cn:"务必着陆确实。",en:"Be sure to stick the landing."};
descriptions["27903"]={cn:"在短短的几分钟里，试着忘记你周围都是讨厌的家伙。",en:"For a few brief moments, try to forget that you\'re surrounded by lousy jerks."};
descriptions["27904"]={cn:"如果滑稽可笑会伤害到你...\n\n你都被送进医院好几次了。",en:"If being ludicrous could actually hurt you...\n\nyou\'d be hospitalized. Several times over."};
descriptions["27905"]={cn:"你的袜子会湿的，但是谁在乎呢。",en:"Your socks will be wet, but who cares."};
descriptions["27906"]={cn:"像鸟一样自由，像风一样快。\n并且没有坐骑带来的麻烦。",en:"Be free as a bird, as fast as the wind.\nBut without the hassle of a mount."};
descriptions["27907"]={cn:"手边有一桶水吗？\n\n\'因为你...\n\n着火了。嘿嘿...嗯哼。",en:"Got a bucket of water handy?\n\n\'Cause you\'re...\n\non fire. Heh heh... Ahem."};
descriptions["27908"]={cn:"即使双脚牢牢地踩在地面上，也终将埋入地面下。",en:"Having your feet firmly on the ground won\'t stop you from ending up six feet under."};
descriptions["27909"]={cn:"它会抛出闪电并喷出蒸汽。\n\n如果人们停止访问你的庇护带，请不要感到震惊。",en:"It tosses lightning bolts and spits out steam.\n\nDon\'t be shocked if people stop visiting your haven bag."};
descriptions["27910"]={cn:"巧克力的香味可以吸引更多游客到你的庇护带里。",en:"The delicious aroma of chocolate could lure a few extra visitors to your haven bag."};
descriptions["27911"]={cn:"如果你害怕的话，抓住那只龙鸟的角，冲过去。",en:"If you ever get scared, just grab the Dragoturkey by the horns and charge on through."};
descriptions["27916"]={cn:"现在你看起来可以吃了。",en:"Now you\'ll look good enough to eat."};
descriptions["27917"]={cn:"在你摇的时候为什么要滚？",en:"Why rock when you can roll?"};
