descriptions["27961"]={cn:"骑着龙很酷，骑着尸龙更酷！",en:"Riding a dragon is cool, but riding a Draghoul is cooler than cool."};
descriptions["27962"]={cn:"没有轮胎就不怕爆胎！",en:"No tires, no risk of a flat!"};
descriptions["27963"]={cn:"令敌人战栗，也令人怀疑你的品味。",en:"This costume will frighten your enemies and will be the end of good taste."};
descriptions["27964"]={cn:"成为那些卡住齿轮的沙粒。",en:"Be the grains of sand in the gears."};
descriptions["27965"]={cn:"你感到如风一般自由。",en:"You\'ll finally feel as free as the wind."};
descriptions["27966"]={cn:"有人抱怨太潮湿，但务实的冒险者会说这是良好的保湿效果。",en:"Some people complain it\'s wet, but pragmatic adventurers say it\'s hydrating."};
descriptions["27967"]={cn:"既保暖又舒适，让夜晚火热起来！",en:"This will keep you nice and warm and help you set the night on fire!"};
descriptions["27968"]={cn:"这件衣服的泥煤味，让你想到许久以前穿着蛛丝内裤洗泥巴浴的时候。",en:"This costume gives off peaty odor that reminds you of a time long past when you would take mud baths in your Arachnee skin underwear."};
descriptions["27969"]={cn:"使用后会启动或关闭终结技。此物品不可堆叠。发动时会从启动的终结技里随机发动一个。",en:"Using this will activate or deactivate the Finisher. The item is not consumed. Random selection among all active Finishers."};
descriptions["27970"]={cn:"使用后会启动或关闭终结技。此物品不可堆叠。发动时会从启动的终结技里随机发动一个。",en:"Using this will activate or deactivate the Finisher. The item is not consumed. Random selection among all active Finishers."};
