descriptions["27972"]={cn:"With shiny fur and sharp fangs, this little creature has it all.",en:"With shiny fur and sharp fangs, this little creature has it all."};
descriptions["27973"]={cn:"This little dragon has sinister ideas sometimes.",en:"This little dragon has sinister ideas sometimes."};
descriptions["27974"]={cn:"A dragon with feathers and a beak... The vendor in the market most likely swindled you.",en:"A dragon with feathers and a beak... The vendor in the market most likely swindled you."};
descriptions["27975"]={cn:"This dragon sleeps with one eye open.",en:"This dragon sleeps with one eye open."};
descriptions["27976"]={cn:"Too cute to be honest, this particular dragon is probably hiding a terrible secret, like a passion for sewing or collecting post cards.",en:"Too cute to be honest, this particular dragon is probably hiding a terrible secret, like a passion for sewing or collecting post cards."};
descriptions["27977"]={cn:"This dragon\'s little brain is similar to that of fowl.\nWith it by your side, you\'ll double your IQ.",en:"This dragon\'s little brain is similar to that of fowl.\nWith it by your side, you\'ll double your IQ."};
descriptions["27978"]={cn:"His gaze says a lot. But about what?\nIt\'s up to you to find out.",en:"His gaze says a lot. But about what?\nIt\'s up to you to find out."};
descriptions["27979"]={cn:"What if you mixed the contents of these two vials?",en:"What if you mixed the contents of these two vials?"};
descriptions["27980"]={cn:"Wake the dragon slumbering within you.",en:"Wake the dragon slumbering within you."};
descriptions["27981"]={cn:"Protect yourself when you go out.",en:"Protect yourself when you go out."};
descriptions["27982"]={cn:"让你看起来更加荒谬。\n\n并非不可能。",en:"You\'ll look even more ridiculous than usual.\n\nIt\'s possible."};
descriptions["27984"]={cn:"收集 100 块碎片，合成阿玛克纳船长盾牌。",en:"Collect 100 of these fragments to create a Captain Amakna Shield."};
descriptions["27985"]={cn:"收集 100 块碎片，合成科瓦克靴子。",en:"Collect 100 of these fragments to create a pair of Kovak\'s Boots."};
descriptions["27986"]={cn:"收集 100 块碎片，合成地衣肩甲。",en:"Collect 100 of these fragments to create Lichen\'s Epaulettes."};
descriptions["27987"]={cn:"收集 100 块碎片，合成卓斯战士头盔。",en:"Collect 100 of these fragments to create a Zoth Warrior Helmet."};
descriptions["27992"]={cn:"打开取得地下城排名的奖励！\n\n\n\n25% 机率取得一件外观物品\n\n100% 机率取得 1 份附魔碎片、奖章或重铸石\n\n1% 机率取得一个史诗或遗物升华",en:"Open it to find out what you\'ve won by being ranked among the best in the dungeon!\n\n25% chance of obtaining a cosmetic item\n100% chance of obtaining 1 set of shards, tokens, or transmutations\n1% chance of getting an epic or relic Sublimation"};
descriptions["27993"]={cn:"打开取得地下城排名的奖励！\n\n\n\n50% 机率取得一件外观物品\n\n100% 机率取得 3 份附魔碎片、奖章或重铸石\n\n3% 机率取得一个史诗或遗物升华",en:"Open it to find out what you\'ve won by being ranked among the best in the dungeon!\n\n50% chance of obtaining a cosmetic item\n100% chance of obtaining 3 sets of shards, tokens, or transmutations\n3% chance of getting an epic or relic Sublimation"};
descriptions["27994"]={cn:"打开取得地下城排名的奖励！\n\n\n\n90% 机率取得一件外观物品\n\n100% 机率取得 6 份附魔碎片、奖章或重铸石\n\n5% 机率取得一个史诗或遗物升华",en:"Open it to find out what you\'ve won by being ranked among the best in the dungeon!\n\n90% chance of obtaining a cosmetic item\n100% chance of obtaining 6 sets of shards, tokens, or transmutations\n5% chance of getting an epic or relic Sublimation"};
descriptions["27995"]={cn:"拿雪狼当皮草之前，至少先要杀死它吧！",en:"Better not try wearing a Snowfoux\'s pelt before killing it!"};
descriptions["27996"]={cn:"很久以前，雪封村经常遭受雪狼的侵袭。村民们即便死后变成了北地骸骨，也无法忘记这场战斗。他们再次对雪狼发动了攻击！",en:"In the past, the Snowbound Village was under constant attack by Snowfoux. The Northern Chafers, former villagers who are now dead, never forgot this affront, and, many years later, launched an attack on them!"};
descriptions["27997"]={cn:"北地骸骨老是穿着一身雪狼皮毛出来活动，迪波尔神父经常误以为是真的雪狼来了！",en:"The Northern Chafers got the better of the Snowfoux and proudly wear their skins. Father Deepboar is constantly mistaking them for actual Snowfoux!"};
descriptions["28019"]={cn:"美丽记忆，永久珍藏。",en:"A nice trophy for your personal collection."};
