descriptions["28027"]={cn:"这套服装证明你解剖的生物远超需要的数量！",en:"This costume proves you\'ve dissected more than your fair share of creatures!"};
descriptions["28028"]={cn:"这件咒符带有菲卡的庇护，能在一定时间内从塔的影响下保护你。",en:"This talisman was made from Feca\'s Aegis. It will protect you from the Tower\'s influence for some time."};
