descriptions["28033"]={cn:"你以为是你烤面包，但很可能是面包烤你。",en:"You thought you\'d roast this toast, but it might roast you instead."};
descriptions["28034"]={cn:"真是可爱的博饼，美味且涂满了鲜奶油！",en:"What a lovely craipe, all taisty and covered in waiped craime!"};
descriptions["28035"]={cn:"摸起来的质感让人想到腐肉。",en:"The texture of this Earth-Earth is reminiscent of decomposing flesh."};
descriptions["28036"]={cn:"似乎会动的塔泥，微妙的东西。",en:"Towpeat that seems to move, the tricky thing."};
descriptions["28037"]={cn:"在这塔晶中能看到微小的班点。",en:"You can see tiny flecks of towermaline in this aventowerine."};
descriptions["28038"]={cn:"如预想一般坚固，没有什么特别的奇怪之处。",en:"Sturdy as expected, there\'s nothing off-the-wall about this wall."};
