descriptions["28042"]={cn:"Your beloved Bow Meows can scratch to their hearts\' content with this pet store classic. Make sure you put it away or hide it well if you invite Ecaflips into your haven bag.",en:"Your beloved Bow Meows can scratch to their hearts\' content with this pet store classic. Make sure you put it away or hide it well if you invite Ecaflips into your haven bag."};
descriptions["28043"]={cn:"Your adored Bow Wows won\'t be forced to take up all the space in your bed anymore. Even better, this doghouse is great for those who don\'t have pets: it makes a wonderful guesthouse for your Ouginak friends who\'ve come for an extended visit.",en:"Your adored Bow Wows won\'t be forced to take up all the space in your bed anymore. Even better, this doghouse is great for those who don\'t have pets: it makes a wonderful guesthouse for your Ouginak friends who\'ve come for an extended visit."};
descriptions["28044"]={cn:"这件披风坚韧、光亮而且棘手，让你想起了以前学校的女老师。\n纪念你仍然在每天学习新知识的时光。",en:"Rigid, luminous and prickly, this cloak reminds you of an old schoolmarm.\nIt\'s a souvenir of the time when you still learned something new every day."};
