descriptions["28062"]={cn:"装饰在这护符上的小石头是在矿石之塔中一个生物的胃里发现的。感到厌恶和感到刺激间的界限有时非常狭窄。",en:"The tiny stones adorning this amulet were found in the stomach of a creature in the Mineral Tower. The line between repulsive and exciting is sometimes very thin."};
