descriptions["28070"]={cn:"会在队友接近临终之时，发出细微的哨声。这样一来，你就有时间可以将包包腾出空间放他们的物品。",en:"This lets off a little whistle when an ally is nearing their last hour. That way, you have time to make room in your bag before relieving your ally of their personal effects."};
