descriptions["28073"]={cn:"它以对手临终时的气息为食。为了确保它不会饿死，你有两种选择：战斗获胜，或是讲烂笑话。",en:"It feeds on your opponents\' last sighs. To make sure it doesn\'t starve to death, you have two options: win your battles or tell bad jokes."};
