descriptions["28076"]={cn:"这双靴子具有神奇魔力 - 无论你多不常洗袜子，它都能轻易消除掉脚臭。实际上是假的，没有任何一种魔力足以做到这一点。",en:"These boots are absolutely magical! They easily neutralize foot odor no matter how rarely you wash your socks. That\'s not really true. No magic is powerful enough to do that."};
