descriptions["28078"]={cn:"你不知道附在这根树枝上的东西到底可不可以食用。",en:"You haven\'t a clue as to whether the treats attached to this twig are edible or not."};
descriptions["28079"]={cn:"你不知道附在这根树枝上的东西到底可不可以食用。",en:"You haven\'t a clue as to whether the treats attached to this twig are edible or not."};
descriptions["28080"]={cn:"无论是你细腻的时尚感、协调的步态还是臀部的优雅摆动，无不令各地的冒险者为之嫉妒。光是看着你就是一种视觉的飨宴。",en:"Adventurers everywhere will be jealous of your exquisite fashion sense, your harmonious gait, and the graceful way you sway your hips. The sight of you is a treat for the eyes."};
descriptions["28081"]={cn:"无论是你细腻的时尚感、协调的步态还是臀部的优雅摆动，无不令各地的冒险者为之嫉妒。光是看着你就是一种视觉的飨宴。",en:"Adventurers everywhere will be jealous of your exquisite fashion sense, your harmonious gait, and the graceful way you sway your hips. The sight of you is a treat for the eyes."};
descriptions["28082"]={cn:"某次实验出错之后，变成了这件小珠宝开启第二生。许多冒险者都认得这件物品。",en:"After an experiment gone wrong, this got a second chance at life as a small jewel. Many an adventurer can identify with this item."};
descriptions["28083"]={cn:"某次实验出错之后，变成了这件小珠宝开启第二生。许多冒险者都认得这件物品。",en:"After an experiment gone wrong, this got a second chance at life as a small jewel. Many an adventurer can identify with this item."};
descriptions["28084"]={cn:"这顶帽子是在一座神庙深处发现的，以前能够射出雷射光线。",en:"This headgear found in the depths of a sanctuary used to be able to shoot rays of light."};
descriptions["28085"]={cn:"这顶帽子是在一座神庙深处发现的，以前能够射出雷射光线。",en:"This headgear found in the depths of a sanctuary used to be able to shoot rays of light."};
descriptions["28086"]={cn:"Vesti un bastonu\nPari un baronu.\nVesti una tama\nPari una dama.",en:"Vesti un bastonu\nPari un baronu.\nVesti una tama\nPari una dama."};
descriptions["28087"]={cn:"Vesti un bastonu\nPari un baronu.\nVesti una tama\nPari una dama.",en:"Vesti un bastonu\nPari un baronu.\nVesti una tama\nPari una dama."};
descriptions["28088"]={cn:"它的持有者把箭射完时，会拿弓来当作法杖使。",en:"When its owner ran out of arrows, they used the bow as a staff."};
descriptions["28089"]={cn:"“跟着那件衣服安息吧！”这是那位裁缝在你偷走这件遗物离开时说的最后一句话。那到底是威胁还是预告呢？",en:"\"Rest in peace with that vest!\" That\'s the last thing the tailor you stole this relic from said as you left with it. But was it a threat or a promise?"};
descriptions["28090"]={cn:"能够牢牢地束住你的裤子，再也不怕光屁股了。\n但只有你说得上来这到底是免于出糗还是限制了你的风格。",en:"It\'ll hold up your trousers better than anything else. No more bare-bottomed spankings for you.\nBut only you can say whether this spares you from humiliation or cramps your style."};
descriptions["28091"]={cn:"这枚徽章的光洁色泽能蒙蔽你的双眼。",en:"This emblem can blind you with its alabaster hue."};
descriptions["28092"]={cn:"这枚徽章显然受到太多日晒了。",en:"This emblem clearly spent too much time in the sun."};
descriptions["28093"]={cn:"要有钢铁一般的胆量才有办法抢尽锋头。",en:"You\'ll need to steel your nerves to steal the show."};
descriptions["28094"]={cn:"徽章上有着隐约浮现的铭文，看起来显然是某种双关语。但你看不懂，而且也拒绝让别人给你解释。",en:"There is a faint inscription on this emblem. A pun of some sort, apparently. But you don\'t get it and you refuse to let anyone explain it to you."};
descriptions["28095"]={cn:"这块石碑给你的庇护袋加上新的机制，让人更难进入。",en:"This stele adds a new mechanic to your haven bag, making it considerably harder to get in."};
descriptions["28096"]={cn:"将这块石碑放在庇护袋里，会使海尔伯格伯爵出现。他会将你在庇护袋里的移动全部反转。",en:"Placed in your haven bag, this stele causes Count Harebourg to appear. He\'ll reverse all your movements while you\'re inside."};
descriptions["28097"]={cn:"戴上这顶头盔，解放你最原始的本能。这会有什么错呢？",en:"Once you equip this helmet, you\'ll be able to let your most basic instincts roam free. What could possibly go wrong?"};
descriptions["28098"]={cn:"收集 100 块碎片，合成安息上衣。",en:"Collect 100 of these fragments to create a Rest Vest."};
descriptions["28099"]={cn:"收集 100 块碎片，合成真力腰带。",en:"Collect 100 of these fragments to create a True Power Belt.."};
descriptions["28102"]={cn:"The lenses on its goggles are opaque. There\'s no safety belt. Good luck!",en:"The lenses on its goggles are opaque. There\'s no safety belt. Good luck!"};
descriptions["28103"]={cn:"The saddle is all wet, but at least it\'s not your fault this time.",en:"The saddle is all wet, but at least it\'s not your fault this time."};
descriptions["28104"]={cn:"You and your mount are literally trailblazers.",en:"You and your mount are literally trailblazers."};
descriptions["28105"]={cn:"Your heroic appearance on the back of this mount will move even the most stone-hearted observer. There\'s no denying it. You rock.",en:"Your heroic appearance on the back of this mount will move even the most stone-hearted observer. There\'s no denying it. You rock."};
descriptions["28106"]={cn:"Foul-smelling monster seeks fine-smelling master.",en:"Foul-smelling monster seeks fine-smelling master."};
descriptions["28107"]={cn:"下次穿上山玩捉迷藏。",en:"For your next game of hide-and-seek with a mountain."};
descriptions["28108"]={cn:"防尘但可能会生锈。",en:"Protects you in dust-ups, but may tend to rust up."};
descriptions["28109"]={cn:"不想被泪水淹没的话，你会想要这件服装的。",en:"You\'ll want this if you don\'t want it all to end in tears."};
descriptions["28110"]={cn:"战斗不加思索，或是弄出砰然巨响。",en:"Jump into the fight without thinking, or sink in taking quite a loud thumping."};
descriptions["28111"]={cn:"温和有礼...现在来说的话。",en:"Sweet and well-behaved... for now."};
descriptions["28112"]={cn:"总算能自由飞翔了。",en:"At last, you can finally fly free."};
