descriptions["28118"]={cn:"使用后会启动或关闭终结技。此物品不可堆叠。发动时会从启动的终结技里随机发动一个。",en:"Using this will activate or deactivate the Finisher. The item is not consumed. Random selection among all active Finishers."};
descriptions["28119"]={cn:"使用后会启动或关闭终结技。此物品不可堆叠。发动时会从启动的终结技里随机发动一个。",en:"Using this will activate or deactivate the Finisher. This item is not consumed. Random selection among all active Finishers."};
descriptions["28120"]={cn:"可能会稍微弄得一团乱。",en:"This might make a bit of a mess."};
descriptions["28121"]={cn:"在你脚下出现可爱的小水晶，感觉有点古怪。",en:"Lovely little crystals appear under your feet. It\'s oddly disquieting."};
descriptions["28122"]={cn:"能够改变造型，但战争...战争永远不变。",en:"Change your skin if you like, but war... war never changes."};
descriptions["28123"]={cn:"造型俐落的龙鸟比一般龙鸟有魅力。\n但依然只是只大鸟。",en:"A sharp-dressed Dragoturkey has more charm than a regular Dragoturkey.\nBut it\'s still just a big turkey."};
descriptions["28124"]={cn:"From its atrophied wings, it\'s clear that this species hasn\'t flown for at least a hundred generations...\nAre you as flabbergasted as we are?",en:"From its atrophied wings, it\'s clear that this species hasn\'t flown for at least a hundred generations...\nAre you as flabbergasted as we are?"};
descriptions["28125"]={cn:"如预想一般坚固，没有什么特别的奇怪之处。",en:"Sturdy as expected, there\'s nothing off-the-wall about this wall."};
