descriptions["28322"]={cn:"这件护身符属于一名文盲战士，一名现今被认为是发明了学校的人。",en:"This talisman belonged to an illiterate warrior who, it is now said, invented school."};
descriptions["28323"]={cn:"这顶帽子曾属于著名的酷奇，以他鲜为人知的缺点和传奇般的好心情而闻名。之后这顶帽子由艾克希佩戴，他是一个充满幽默感的骑士，并且也同样出色，他的壮举要花很长时间才能在这里列出。尽管如此，这位影子英雄仍为了十二世界的利益而暗中做了许多大事。",en:"This headgear once belonged to the famous Koolich, renowned for his clay feet and his legendary good mood. It was then worn by Exi, a good-humored Iop who was just as remarkable, and whose feats would take far too long to list here. Nevertheless, this hero of the shadows has done many a great deed in secret for the good of the World of Twelve."};
descriptions["28324"]={cn:"收集 100 块碎片，合成酷奇帽。",en:"Collect 100 of these fragments to create a Koolich Headgear."};
descriptions["28325"]={cn:"适合用来回避打不赢的架或是尴尬的讨论。",en:"Perfect for avoiding unwinnable fights or embarrassing discussions."};
descriptions["28326"]={cn:"就算找上一辈子，也无法在上面找到一点瑕疵。\n但这不适用于你的朋友。",en:"Even if you searched all your life, you\'d never find a single flaw in it.\nThe same can\'t be said about your friends, however."};
descriptions["28327"]={cn:"收集 100 块碎片，合成珍惜披风。",en:"Collect 100 of these fragments to create a Cherished Cloak."};
descriptions["28328"]={cn:"曾属于一名占有欲有点太强的女人。",en:"It once belonged to a woman who was a little too possessive."};
descriptions["28329"]={cn:"见过这枚戒指的人都忘不了它，它也不曾遗忘任何人。",en:"No one who has seen this ring has ever forgotten it. It has never forgotten anyone either."};
descriptions["28330"]={cn:"收集 100 块碎片，合成最后之戒。",en:"Collect 100 of these fragments to create a Last Ring."};
descriptions["28331"]={cn:"这种坚韧的皮革不导电，你可以在雷雨天穿出去。别把这话当真。",en:"This tough leather doesn\'t conduct electricity. You should be okay wearing it out in a lightning storm, but don\'t take our word for it."};
descriptions["28332"]={cn:"这些异常危险的尖刺曾会被拿来当棒针用。人们会拿给他们想要巧妙除掉的笨拙祖母使用。噢，真是不幸的意外！",en:"These especially dangerous spikes were once used as knitting needles. People often gave them to clumsy grandmothers they wanted to discreetly do away with. Oh, what an unfortunate accident!"};
descriptions["28333"]={cn:"这是由残缺的蒂和可笑的马尾所产生的怪异组合。也许喧嚣龟是死于嘲弄，而非撕裂伤？",en:"This is a grotesque combination of a torn-out pedicle and a ridiculous ponytail. Perhaps the ridicule killed the Tortumult rather than the tearing-out?"};
descriptions["28334"]={cn:"你没闻过衰老又腐烂的爬壳类是什么味道，是吗？那你现在闻闻看这臭气熏天的种子就知道了。",en:"You don\'t know what old, rotten Scramshell smells like, do you? Well now you can find out with this surprisingly stinky seed."};
descriptions["28335"]={cn:"这能做成料理？一定是有人在开你玩笑。",en:"They\'re serving this as a dish? Someone must be pulling your leg."};
descriptions["28336"]={cn:"就算食物柜里什么都不剩了，你也还有这个。",en:"Even if there\'s nothing left in the pantry, you\'ve still got this."};
descriptions["28337"]={cn:"拿来擦你珍贵的肌肤或拿去做家务，你自己选择。",en:"Rub this on your beloved\'s skin or do the housework with it. The choice is yours."};
descriptions["28338"]={cn:"这根刺能给任何冷饮添加一份冰镇惊喜！",en:"This stinger adds an ice surprise to any cool drink!"};
descriptions["28339"]={cn:"何不将手伸进蜂巢里挖出蜂蜜大口吮指？也许蜜蜂没有想要拿回来...",en:"Why not greedily lick your fingers after touching this honeycomb? The bees probably don\'t want it back..."};
descriptions["28340"]={cn:"与蜂蜜的质感相同，但并不是蜂蜜。",en:"It\'s got the same texture as honey, but it\'s not actually honey."};
descriptions["28341"]={cn:"保证至少五年不用清洗。",en:"Guaranteed not to need washing for at least five years."};
descriptions["28342"]={cn:"又肥又带血，任何人都满意。",en:"It\'s fatty and bloody, all anyone needs to be happy."};
descriptions["28343"]={cn:"企鹅浮冰几乎到处都能找到这些小鱼。",en:"You can find these Snappers almost everywhere around the Pingwins\' Ice Floe."};
descriptions["28344"]={cn:"嘘独王国是先有企鹅还是先有蛋？",en:"Which came first to the Shhhudoku Kingdom: the Pingwin or the egg?"};
descriptions["28345"]={cn:"没人知道为什么力士海象长了这么一对尖牙，却又还要戴着尖刺项圈。肯定只需要一样就好了啊！",en:"No one really knows why the Sumorse wears a spiked collar when it\'s already got such long, pointed teeth. One or the other, surely!"};
descriptions["28346"]={cn:"真可爱！但仅限还小的时候。",en:"They\'re so cute! But only while they\'re little."};
descriptions["28347"]={cn:"还带着蹼，因此可以用来搅拌软骨汤。好吃。",en:"It\'s webbed and can therefore be used to stir cartilage soup. Yumm."};
descriptions["28348"]={cn:"含有让你长大变壮所需的一切蛋白质。",en:"It contains all the protein you need to grow big and strong."};
