descriptions["28360"]={cn:"如果今年没有收到朋友的礼物，那肯定不是交通工具的问题。",en:"If you don\'t get your friends gifts this year, it won\'t be for a lack of transportation."};
descriptions["28361"]={cn:"如果不想被人听见，那就穿上这件服装。",en:"Wear this if you don\'t want to be heard."};
descriptions["28362"]={cn:"你现在可以穿得跟那位刽子手一样了。\n可以在阿斯图布酒馆将这件服装换成完整版。",en:"You can finally dress up as a butcher.\nThis costume can be traded in for the complete version at the machine in the Astrub Inn."};
descriptions["28363"]={cn:"有人问过你为什么看起来像个钟表匠吗？",en:"Has anyone ever asked you why you look like a clockmaker?"};
descriptions["28364"]={cn:"给那些讨厌浪费时间在晚上脱装又要在早上着装的人。",en:"This is for all those who hate wasting time getting undressed at night and getting dressed in the morning."};
descriptions["28365"]={cn:"你总是梦想着探索新的次元，但你从未踏出过村庄一步。",en:"You\'ve always dreamed of exploring new dimensions, but you\'ve never even left your village."};
descriptions["28366"]={cn:"别在打猎时穿这件服装，除非你想把猎物吓跑并成为别人的练习目标。",en:"Don\'t wear this while hunting, unless you want to scare away your prey and become someone\'s target practice."};
descriptions["28367"]={cn:"有些人喜欢它的朴素，他们要不是色盲就是没有时尚感。",en:"Some people like it for its plainness. They must all either be colorblind or have no fashion sense."};
descriptions["28368"]={cn:"你还是会喘不过气。",en:"It might still leave you gasping for air."};
descriptions["28369"]={cn:"进退两喵。",en:"Looks like you\'re stuck between a stone block and a hard place."};
descriptions["28370"]={cn:"骤雨将来...",en:"It\'s gonna rain Bow Meows and Bow Wows..."};
descriptions["28371"]={cn:"可能会烧掉手指。",en:"You might get your fingers burned domesticating this creature."};
descriptions["28372"]={cn:"立正！",en:"Atten-shush!"};
descriptions["28374"]={cn:"若是能成为众人焦点，何需蹑手蹑脚？",en:"Why go around all discreetly when you can draw everyone\'s gaze to you?"};
descriptions["28375"]={cn:"在人前炫耀这对翅膀，可能会让你满嘴羽毛。",en:"You might end up spitting feathers if you keep flaunting these fabulous wings in front of people."};
