descriptions["28380"]={cn:"孤旷传细语，\n寒天朔风催日短，\n徐徐门扉开。",en:"A distant murmur,\nWinter breathes from far away,\nThe lock opens up."};
descriptions["28381"]={cn:"袅袅兮秋风，\n晨钟锵兮木叶下，\n瑟瑟金锁鸣。",en:"The wind blows softly,\nHear an autumn clunk ring out:\nA lock resounding."};
descriptions["28382"]={cn:"仲夏苦夜短，\n开轩却闻寂静言，\n杳杳前路展。",en:"Carrying the word,\nSummer\'s word is whispered soft:\nYou\'re on your way now."};
