descriptions["28392"]={cn:"艾葛贝瑞尔交给你的一颗松青龙蛋。孵化出来的，会是博格罗特那样为十二世界带来恐惧的危害，亦或是这世界坚韧的象征？",en:"A Turquoise Dofus given by Aguabrial. If it hatches, could it bring back a threat as terrible as Bolgrot to the World of Twelve? Or perhaps it\'s a symbol of the world\'s resilience?"};
descriptions["28393"]={cn:"这本书是在企鹅浮冰上发现的奇怪铭文翻译后的译文。",en:"This book is a translation of the strange inscriptions found at the Pingwins\' Ice Floe."};
