descriptions["28406"]={cn:"受到末日而改变的某个世界的样貌。",en:"This is the face of a world that was changed by the Eliocalypse."};
descriptions["28407"]={cn:"踏上去时会对你低语。",en:"It whispers when you walk on it."};
descriptions["28408"]={cn:"这个工匠配方，让你学会制作数种低语石墙。",en:"This blueprint will teach you the recipe for several Whispered Walls for the Handyman profession."};
descriptions["28409"]={cn:"令人无法将目光移开这顶帽子。",en:"You won\'t be able to take your eyes off this hat."};
descriptions["28410"]={cn:"穿上这件上衣后，你所说的一切都会变得有说服力，并让他人崇拜你。",en:"Put on this jacket and everything you say will be eloquent and achieve cult status."};
descriptions["28411"]={cn:"一件死人身上的破旧披风，肯定是幸运之兆。",en:"An old, worn cloak off a dead man. A lucky omen no doubt."};
descriptions["28412"]={cn:"不，这件背心跟征服了撕裂荒野的冒险者无关，它是因为在重复的洗涤中被撕裂而获得了这个名字。",en:"No, this vest didn\'t belong to an adventurer out to conquer the Vild Vest. It earned this nickname by getting torn in the wash. Repeatedly."};
descriptions["28413"]={cn:"西部英雄的必备配件，不幸的是，也是抢匪的配件。",en:"An essential accessory for somber heroes everywhere. Too bad for you, it\'s also the mark of sober heroes everywhere."};
descriptions["28414"]={cn:"穿上这双靴子，会在行经之处留下燃烧的足迹。也能燃烧你的敌人。",en:"When you wear these boots, the earth will burn in your tracks. Your enemies too."};
descriptions["28415"]={cn:"你可能会好奇为什么会叫这名字，抬一下肩膀就会知道了。",en:"You\'re probably wondering why they have this name. Shrug your shoulders and your question will be answered."};
descriptions["28417"]={cn:"艾葛贝瑞尔交给你的一颗松青龙蛋。孵化出来的，会是博格罗特那样为十二世界带来恐惧的危害，亦或是这世界坚韧的象征？",en:"A Turquoise Dofus given by Aguabrial. If it hatches, could it bring back a threat as terrible as Bolgrot to the World of Twelve? Or perhaps it\'s a symbol of the world\'s resilience?"};
