descriptions["28736"]={cn:"卷轴上贴着皇家封印。内容肯定很重要。",en:"This scroll is sealed with the royal stamp. It must say something important."};
descriptions["28737"]={cn:"由TNT兄弟制造的烈性炸药！轰！",en:"The famous oil created by brothers Turp and Tyne. It\'s a turp!"};
descriptions["28738"]={cn:"只生长在充满悲伤和遗憾之处的独特树木。",en:"This unique tree only grows in places rife with sadness and regret."};
descriptions["28739"]={cn:"让看着它的人感到绝望。",en:"This bit of wood makes anyone who looks at it despair."};
descriptions["28740"]={cn:"很久以前就失去了希望，被懊悔和悔恨所消耗，而后重生为一棵树。",en:"This wood was a being that lost all hope long ago. It was consumed by chagrin and regret, but was reborn as a tree."};
descriptions["28741"]={cn:"实际上并不存在，只是你疯狂之下的产物。",en:"This cutting doesn\'t really exist. It is but the fruit of your insanity."};
descriptions["28742"]={cn:"无论你如何努力，都无法描述这件东西。",en:"No matter how much effort you put in, you can\'t describe this item."};
descriptions["28743"]={cn:"当事情进展顺利时，其实并不那么顺利；当事情变得糟糕时，其实并不那么糟糕。",en:"When things are going well, they\'re not that well. When things are going bad, they\'re not that bad."};
descriptions["28744"]={cn:"无论种在何处，请确保不要用盐水来浇水。",en:"Wherever you eventually plant this seed, make sure you don\'t water it with salt water."};
descriptions["28745"]={cn:"无论故事里是怎么说的，吃下这果实并不会带给你任何特殊的力量。",en:"Despite what the stories say, eating this fruit won\'t give you any special powers."};
descriptions["28746"]={cn:"出奇地富有弹性。",en:"This fruit is strangely flexible."};
descriptions["28747"]={cn:"与恶魔果实不同，只能在盐度非常高的环境生长。",en:"Unlike the Demon Fruit, this seed can only grow in very salty environments."};
descriptions["28748"]={cn:"这在魔之界发现的豆子，会毫不犹豫地帮助你并支持你的努力，这正是它的邪恶名字的由来。",en:"This bean found in the Shustuft Crust won\'t hesitate to help you and support you in your efforts. And that\'s precisely how it got its evil name."};
descriptions["28749"]={cn:"真的，很善良。",en:"It\'s true. It is nice."};
descriptions["28750"]={cn:"与其他花一起生长时，长得最好（它喜欢啃那些花当点心）。",en:"This seed grows best alongside other flowers (it likes to nibble on them between meals)."};
descriptions["28751"]={cn:"据说吃下去会缩短寿命。（你知道的，如果你不知道家庭晚餐要准备什么...说说而已。）",en:"It\'s said that eating this can shorten you life expectancy. (You know, in case you\'re short on ideas for the next family dinner... Just saying.)"};
descriptions["28752"]={cn:"会会让让你你声声音音颤颤抖抖。",en:"This this plant plant can can give give you you a a horrible horrible verbal verbal tic tic."};
descriptions["28753"]={cn:"在由大量痛苦所浇灌过的土壤中生长得最好。",en:"This seed grows best in soil fertilized with heavy doses of suffering."};
descriptions["28754"]={cn:"你有想过会在魔之界这样的环境中，找到阿斯图布蓝蓟的远亲吗？",en:"Did you think you\'d find this distant cousin of the Astrubian thistle in an environment such as the Shustuft Crust?"};
descriptions["28755"]={cn:"非常迷人。",en:"This thistle is extremely charming."};
descriptions["28756"]={cn:"拥有让你每过一秒就老一秒的能力。",en:"This stone has the power to make you one second older with every second that passes."};
descriptions["28757"]={cn:"非常适合美丽的墓碑。",en:"Perfect for beautiful tombs."};
descriptions["28758"]={cn:"不要嘲讽它。",en:"Do not taunt the Symbiotic Stone."};
descriptions["28759"]={cn:"像征着魔之界交织着的那股奇特氛围。",en:"This stone symbolizes the strange interlacing of ambiances in the Shustuft Crust."};
descriptions["28760"]={cn:"非常具有攻击性的恶魔鱼。",en:"This demonic fish is very aggressive."};
descriptions["28761"]={cn:"会将陆地生物拖入水中吞噬。",en:"It draws land creatures into the water in order to devour them."};
descriptions["28762"]={cn:"能够驾轻就熟地编造故事，有点像是政客。",en:"He can spin a tale like nobody\'s business, a bit like any politician."};
descriptions["28763"]={cn:"能够驾轻就熟地编造故事，有点像是记者。",en:"He can spin a tale like nobody\'s business, a bit like any journalist."};
descriptions["28765"]={cn:"并不保暖，因为北地人的太阳不在天上，而是在心中。",en:"It won\'t keep you warm because Nordic peoples carry the sun that they don\'t have in the sky in their hearts."};
descriptions["28766"]={cn:"给那些以为自己属于好人那一方的人。\n真相会使人难以接受。",en:"This costume is for those who think they\'re one of the good guys.\nThe truth will be hard to accept."};
descriptions["28767"]={cn:"绩效制的工作，至少听说是这样的。",en:"Pay merits work, or so they say."};
descriptions["28768"]={cn:"那些即将满身脏污的人向你敬礼。",en:"Those who are about to get dirty salute you."};
descriptions["28769"]={cn:"如果她能烧，她就是木头做的。\n如果她是木头做的，她要不是只鸭子就是个女巫。\n除非她能浮起来。",en:"If she burns, she\'s made of wood.\nIf she\'s made of wood, she\'s a duck or a witch.\nUnless she floats."};
descriptions["28770"]={cn:"有翼的蛇还是长角的龙？\n有些问题最好还是不要解答。",en:"Winged snake or horned dragon?\nSome questions are better left unanswered."};
descriptions["28771"]={cn:"用以解锁此一宠物造型。",en:"Can be used to unlock this pet skin."};
descriptions["28772"]={cn:"这血迹是谁留下来的呢？",en:"Whoever could have left those traces of blood?"};
descriptions["28773"]={cn:"有你在身边，总是令人来电。",en:"The mood will be nothing short of electric with you around."};
descriptions["28774"]={cn:"花在重训上的那些时间能挽救你的性命吗？\n大概无法。",en:"Will all those hours of weight training save your life?\nProbably not."};
descriptions["28775"]={cn:"礼貌而又尊重，适用于各种场合。",en:"Polite and respectful in all circumstances."};
descriptions["28776"]={cn:"“我从小就想当个超级英雄。”",en:"\"I wanted to be a superhero as a kid.\""};
descriptions["28777"]={cn:"阿玛克纳降临于世！",en:"Amakna is Incarnam on Earth!"};
descriptions["28778"]={cn:"微小的一簇草不禁让你精神一振！",en:"The smallest tuft of grass can\'t help but lift your spirits!"};
descriptions["28779"]={cn:"看看这些石头！看看这些披风！我是说，那里真的有金矿！",en:"Look at these rocks! Look at these capes! What I mean is, these are real gold mines!"};
descriptions["28780"]={cn:"每当我想念童年以及那片洒在海上的阳光时，就想去见你！",en:"When I long for childhood and the sun shining on the sea, you\'re the one I go to see!"};
descriptions["28781"]={cn:"自然，维持自然。",en:"Nature, naturally."};
descriptions["28782"]={cn:"盗贼经常被指责是讨厌的小偷，但失去的时间才是最糟糕的。这说的是被偷走的爱、我的健康和我的鞋子。",en:"Rogues are often accused of being nasty thieves, but time is the worst of them all. It\'s stolen love, my health, and my shoes."};
descriptions["28783"]={cn:"很久无法摇滚了，但还是能坐上去。某方面来说有点像是你童年的梦想。",en:"It hasn\'t been able to rock for a very long time, but at least you can still sit in it. A bit like your childhood dreams, in a way."};
descriptions["28784"]={cn:"这张小长凳是不是很可爱啊？",en:"Isn\'t this little bench just too cute?"};
descriptions["28785"]={cn:"这是一张优质的金属圆凳，非常地耐用。",en:"Here is a superb metal stool. It can take a beating."};
descriptions["28786"]={cn:"不同于一般有脚的圆凳，这张圆凳的使用方式比较麻烦。",en:"Unlike normal stools with legs, this stool can only be used in a convoluted manner."};
descriptions["28787"]={cn:"如果知识就是武器，那很多人都是赤手空拳。",en:"If knowledge is a weapon, many go unarmed."};
descriptions["28788"]={cn:"有些人试图复制出这把扶手椅，希望能吸引像米兰达一样容光焕发的幸运猫。",en:"Some have tried to reproduce this armchair in the futile hope of attracting an Ecaflipette as radiant as Miranda."};
descriptions["28789"]={cn:"这把钥匙能用来进入寒冰终极次元裂缝进行战斗。",en:"This key can be used to start a fight in the ultimate rift in Frigost."};
descriptions["28790"]={cn:"这把钥匙能用来进入泽尼特山终极次元裂缝进行战斗。",en:"This key can be used to start a fight in the ultimate rift on Mount Zinit."};
descriptions["28791"]={cn:"使用魔药来启动或解除光环。该魔药无法被消耗。",en:"Using this potion will activate or deactivate your aura. The potion is not consumed."};
descriptions["28792"]={cn:"就是一块石头！",en:"Rock on!"};
descriptions["28793"]={cn:"你喜欢的话可以玩弹珠。",en:"You can play marbles, if that\'s what you enjoy."};
descriptions["28794"]={cn:"这支角有点，呃，冻住了。",en:"This horn is a bit, err, frozen."};
descriptions["28795"]={cn:"该把这支槌子拿去栈板那吗？",en:"Shall we take this mallet to a pallet?"};
descriptions["28796"]={cn:"这些细小的暗影碎片很难取得。",en:"These little shadow fragments were hard to get."};
descriptions["28797"]={cn:"虽然不是神圣玄武岩，但够用了。",en:"This isn\'t sacred basalt, but it\'ll do."};
