descriptions["29011"]={cn:"真他妈有够丑。",en:"She\'s one ugly mofer thucker."};
descriptions["29015"]={cn:"介于错综与复杂之间。",en:"Somewhere between convoluted and convolvulus."};
descriptions["29016"]={cn:"非常适合躲在一堆废弃物中。",en:"Perfect for hiding in a pile of cast-offs."};
descriptions["29017"]={cn:"没事时，没人理你。\n出事时，每个人都瞪着你。",en:"When all\'s well, no one pays any attention to you.\nWhen things go wrong, everyone stares at you."};
descriptions["29018"]={cn:"挥舞魔杖并无法让你成为魔术师。",en:"Waving your magic wand around won\'t make you into a magician."};
descriptions["29019"]={cn:"略带一些毛的兽皮，不包含轮廓分明的肌肉。",en:"Skin of a beast and a bit of fur. Well-defined muscles not included."};
descriptions["29020"]={cn:"唱的音准或不准都没有关系，重要的是要有听众。",en:"It doesn\'t matter if you sing in tune or out of tune; all that matters is that you have an audience."};
descriptions["29021"]={cn:"用以解锁此一宠物造型。",en:"Can be used to unlock this pet skin."};
descriptions["29022"]={cn:"另一边有着些什么？",en:"What\'s hiding on the other side?"};
descriptions["29023"]={cn:"可以在下列兑奖机使用此奖章兑换奖励：植种、虚空、恐惧、巨眼、坏灭。",en:"Use the following machines to exchange your tokens for fantastic rewards: Phytomorphs, Voidivions, Horridemons, Streyes, Destroyers."};
descriptions["29024"]={cn:"可以变更 230 级以内装备的元素加成。",en:"Can be used on an item (at level 230 or less) with variable elementary stats to get different stats among those possible."};
descriptions["29025"]={cn:"可以变更 230 级以内装备的元素加成。",en:"Can be used on an item (at level 230 or less) with variable elementary stats to get different stats among those possible."};
descriptions["29026"]={cn:"这片木板能用来制作家具、护甲或武器。",en:"This plank is used to make furniture, armor, or weapons."};
descriptions["29027"]={cn:"这袋面粉用来制作好吃、热呼呼的面包。",en:"This flour is used to make good, warm bread."};
descriptions["29028"]={cn:"这条绳线能用来制作头盔、护符和戒指。",en:"This string is used to craft headgear and helmets, but also amulets and rings."};
descriptions["29029"]={cn:"这块钢能用来制作武器、护甲或装饰。",en:"This steel can be used to craft weapons, armor, or decorations."};
descriptions["29030"]={cn:"这片鱼片能让你制作美味的餐点。",en:"This Tiramisoup lets you make lovely little dishes."};
descriptions["29031"]={cn:"这份精华包含了怪物的灵魂，能把力量注入几乎所有类型的物品。",en:"This essence contains monsters\' souls, and can instill their power into almost all types of items."};
descriptions["29032"]={cn:"用来烹调美味食物的香料。",en:"This spice is used to make lovely little dishes."};
descriptions["29033"]={cn:"用来制作披风和头饰的纤维。",en:"This fiber is mainly used to craft capes and headgear."};
descriptions["29034"]={cn:"用来制作武器的手柄。",en:"This handle is mainly used to make weapons."};
descriptions["29035"]={cn:"用来制作靴子、皮带和包的皮革。",en:"This leather is mainly used to craft boots, belts, and bags."};
descriptions["29036"]={cn:"用来制作胸甲、肩甲以及盾牌。",en:"This plate is mainly used to make breastplates, epaulettes, and shields."};
descriptions["29037"]={cn:"用来制作戒指和护符的宝石。",en:"This gem is mainly used to craft rings and amulets."};
descriptions["29038"]={cn:"用来制作美味面包和炸食物的油。",en:"This oil is used to make good, rich bread, and to fry your ingredients to prepare dishes."};
descriptions["29039"]={cn:"用在木工上的脚架。",en:"This bracket is used in all types of woodwork."};
descriptions["29040"]={cn:"蕴含着在十二世界中无可比拟的力量。",en:"The power this orb contains is unmatched in the World of Twelve."};
descriptions["29041"]={cn:"胶水是用来组合物品的绝佳选择。你可以从 216 到 230 的地图挑战任务中取得。",en:"Souper-Glou is the ideal ingredient to assemble your items. You can get it as a reward for the level 216 to 230 Environmental Quests."};
descriptions["29042"]={cn:"会从内部蚕食你，有点像爱情。",en:"It\'ll eat you up inside, a bit like love."};
descriptions["29043"]={cn:"不，不，恶魔不吃这种面包的。然而，偶尔会有十二世界人将它用于召唤仪式，犯下这种轻率错误的结局，当然是...变成魔族的点心。",en:"No, no, demons don\'t eat this bread. However, some Twelvians occasionally make the rash mistake of using it in summoning rituals, which of course end in... snacks for Shushus."};
descriptions["29044"]={cn:"收集 100 块碎片，合成伊崔尔帽。",en:"Collect 100 of these fragments to create an Eachure Hat."};
descriptions["29045"]={cn:"收集 100 块碎片，合成蜃气护符。",en:"Collect 100 of these fragments to create a Mirage Amulet."};
descriptions["29046"]={cn:"收集 100 块碎片，合成举杯胸甲。",en:"Collect 100 of these fragments to create a Beber Breastplate."};
descriptions["29047"]={cn:"收集 100 块碎片，合成加侬多夫肩甲。",en:"Collect 100 of these fragments to create Galon d\'Orf Epaulettes."};
descriptions["29048"]={cn:"一件古老的遗物，并且有着恐怖的诅咒。但即使如此，冒险者还是会因为那独特的风格而穿上它。十二世界人真是疯了！",en:"The Noh Cape is an ancient relic linked to a terrible curse. But adventurers put it on anyway because of its distinctive style. Twelvians are crazy!"};
descriptions["29049"]={cn:"据说这双靴子十分邪恶，穿上时小心不要被伤害到。",en:"These boots are rumored to be especially mean-spirited. Be careful when wearing them because they might want to harm you."};
descriptions["29050"]={cn:"据说这双靴子十分邪恶，穿上时小心不要被伤害到。",en:"These boots are rumored to be especially mean-spirited. Be careful when wearing them because they might want to harm you."};
descriptions["29051"]={cn:"当心：这枚戒指相当邪恶。",en:"Be careful: This ring is rather vile."};
descriptions["29052"]={cn:"当心：这枚戒指相当邪恶。",en:"Be careful: This ring is rather vile."};
descriptions["29053"]={cn:"戴着这顶面罩时，别期待有人会信任你。",en:"Don\'t expect anyone to trust you when you wear this mask."};
descriptions["29054"]={cn:"戴着这顶面罩时，别期待有人会信任你。",en:"Don\'t expect anyone to trust you when you wear this mask."};
descriptions["29055"]={cn:"由植种魔族的残片制作而成。别理那些跟你说话的声音，那是被腐化的声音。",en:"This amulet is made from a phytomorph fragment. Don\'t pay attention to those voices talking to you; they\'re clearly corrupted."};
descriptions["29056"]={cn:"由植种魔族的残片制作而成。别理那些跟你说话的声音，那是被腐化的声音。",en:"This amulet is made from a phytomorph fragment. Don\'t pay attention to those voices talking to you; they\'re clearly corrupted."};
descriptions["29057"]={cn:"曾属于一名伟大的公爵，他为布拉克玛的海上棚屋传统做出了重要贡献。后来，他在八角环中与死敌里斯卡的比赛中惨败。不幸的是，他信赖的亡魂火指环没能拯救他...",en:"This cloak once belonged to a great duke who made important contributions to the Brakmarian sea shanty tradition. He later suffered a resounding loss in the octagonal ring against his sworn enemy, Riskaa. Unfortunately, his trusty Makabrakfire Ring couldn\'t save him..."};
descriptions["29058"]={cn:"据说，会让穿戴者备受那些以女人味和惊人红胡子而闻名的兽人女法师亲赖。你知道的，现在脱掉它仍为时不晚。",en:"Once upon a time, this headgear was said to make its wearer especially irresistible to female Bwork magi, known for their femininity and prodigious red beards. You know, it\'s still not too late to get rid of it."};
descriptions["29059"]={cn:"经过精心布置的牙齿，可以保护你最敏感的部位，不被盗贼所踢伤。另一方面，你坐下前最好先取下这条腰带。",en:"Its teeth are strategically placed to defend your most sensitive regions from any Rogue who might try to kick you there. On the other hand, you should probably take this belt off before sitting down."};
descriptions["29060"]={cn:"经过精心布置的牙齿，可以保护你最敏感的部位，不被盗贼所踢伤。另一方面，你坐下前最好先取下这条腰带。",en:"Its teeth are strategically placed to defend your most sensitive regions from any Rogue who might try to kick you there. On the other hand, you should probably take this belt off before sitting down."};
