descriptions["29087"]={cn:"如果突然一阵风吹来，内含的大量危险孢子会让附近所有生灵被具有说话能力的奇特蘑菇所感染。其中一些喜欢开玩笑，而另一些则抱怨怪物太容易打败了。",en:"This cloak contains a large number of dangerous spores. If a sudden gust of wind happens to rustle it, all living beings nearby will be infested by strange mushrooms with the ability to speak. Some of them love to crack jokes, while others whine about the monsters being too easy to beat."};
descriptions["29088"]={cn:"如果突然一阵风吹来，内含的大量危险孢子会让附近所有生灵被具有说话能力的奇特蘑菇所感染。其中一些喜欢开玩笑，而另一些则抱怨怪物太容易打败了。",en:"This cloak contains a large number of dangerous spores. If a sudden gust of wind happens to rustle it, all living beings nearby will be infested by strange mushrooms with the ability to speak. Some of them love to crack jokes, while others whine about the monsters being too easy to beat."};
descriptions["29089"]={cn:"如果吃下去，会发现自己被个恶魔缠住。我们知道它看起来像焦糖，但那只是人工色素。",en:"If you try to eat this, you may find yourself haunted by a demon. We know it looks like a caramel, but that\'s just artificial coloring."};
descriptions["29090"]={cn:"如果吃下去，会发现自己被个恶魔缠住。我们知道它看起来像焦糖，但那只是人工色素。",en:"If you try to eat this, you may find yourself haunted by a demon. We know it looks like a caramel, but that\'s just artificial coloring."};
descriptions["29091"]={cn:"这副肩甲会是下次魔族舞会上的焦点。\n只有一个问题 - 每千年才有一次...",en:"These epaulettes will be a hit at the next Shushu ball.\nThere\'s just one problem - they only have one every thousand years..."};
descriptions["29092"]={cn:"这副肩甲会是下次魔族舞会上的焦点。\n只有一个问题 - 每千年才有一次...",en:"These epaulettes will be a hit at the next Shushu ball.\nThere\'s just one problem - they only have one every thousand years..."};
descriptions["29093"]={cn:"能锁螺丝、能调酒、能载萝丝，你永远用不着的多功能工具！",en:"Use it for driving screws, dividing stews, or driving crews to diving schools. The most versatile tool you\'ll never use!"};
