descriptions["29099"]={cn:"原本的主人是一位了不起的战士。他是无数赛事的冠军，他是辨识对手技巧的专家，并会与他们联手来加强自己的力量。可靠且始终忠于自己，他的核心理念是始终遵循自己的信念 - 这种方法为他带来了巨大的成功。\n他诚实而务实，对待朋友严厉而又公正。他会直接说出自己的想法，毫不含糊。在争吵中，如果你不想听到他说“拜托，认真的？！”，最好站在他那一边；他甚至没注意到自己每两句话就会说一次。",en:"Its original owner was a remarkable fighter. A winner of numerous tournaments, he was an expert at recognizing his opponents\' skills, and eventually joined forces with them to complement his own strengths. Reliable and always true to himself, his core principle was to always follow his convictions - an approach that brought him great success.\nHe was honest and pragmatic, and tough yet fair with his friends. He never hesitated to say what he was thinking without mincing his words. In an argument, it was better to be on his side if you didn\'t want to hear him saying \"C\'mon, seriously?!\" every two sentences without even noticing it."};
