descriptions["29102"]={cn:"据说曾属于一位健壮的时间法师，他对自己的工作非常投入。尽管他总是乐于分享实用的资讯，并帮助他的同胞们，但许多人对他的发明并不重视，观众经常在他公开露面时对他大喊大叫。\n他与这顶头盔形影不离，有时会让他的朋友们抓狂。在某次涉及一个农业设备的讨人厌生意后，他甚至和其中一人完全切断了联系...",en:"They say that this headgear once belonged to a robust Xelor who was deeply invested in his work. Though he was always ready to share a helpful tip and help his fellow Twelvians, many people didn\'t think much of his inventions, and audiences often shouted him down at his public appearances. \nHe was totally inseparable from his Tick, and together they sometimes drove their friends crazy. It seems he even cut one of them loose completely after a nasty business involving a piece of farm equipment..."};
