descriptions["29105"]={cn:"曾属于一名治愈者，她的自我意识夸张得离谱，真的认为自己是艾卡菲利神域的女王。但另一方面，她的时尚感则不是开玩笑的，全世界的人都在寻求着她的青睐。\n她与这间披风形影不离，有时会让她的朋友们抓狂。很多人都嫉妒着她，因为她身边总是有最好的人，而且还不怕说出来；事实上，她甚至有点太健谈了。在艾卡菲利神域的一天里，绝对能听到她和精英们闲聊的声音。",en:"This cloak once belonged to an Eniripsa with a preposterously inflated image of herself. She genuinely thought she was the queen of Ecaflipus. Her sense of style, on the other hand, was anything but preposterous, and people all around the world were constantly seeking her favor.\nShe was totally inseparable from her Tock, and together they sometimes drove their friends crazy. Lots of people were jealous of her because she always had the best people around her, and wasn\'t afraid to say it. She was even a bit too talkative, in fact. You couldn\'t spend a day in Ecaflipus without hearing her gossiping with the local elites."};
