descriptions["29107"]={cn:"属于一名勇敢的守护者，以其魅力而闻名；他似乎每周都有一个新女朋友，更不用说他的浪漫信件迷住了无数年轻女性。\n他也是一位非凡的战略家，在同伴的帮助下战胜了世界上最大的威胁。他好斗和好胜的天性使他成为一个可怕的对手，对他来说并不存在失败的选项。传说中他甚至单枪匹马击败了一些伟大的竞技斗士，世人将永远铭记，他在创纪录的时间内击败了当代最伟大的传奇之一。",en:"These epaulettes belongs to a courageous Feca known for his many charms. He seemed to have a new girlfriend every week, not to mention the countless young women he enchanted with his romantic letters.\nHe was also an extraordinary strategist who took down the greatest threats the world had ever faced, with the help of his traveling companions. His combative and competitive nature made him a fearsome opponent, as defeat was not an option for him. Legend has it that he even single-handedly bested some of the greatest arena fighters, and will always be remembered for having subjected one of the Wakfu era\'s greatest legends to a humiliating defeat in record time."};
