descriptions["29109"]={cn:"一个独特的符号，让愤怒的游牧民族，确认彼此的身份。",en:"A distinctive symbol that allows angry nomads to identify themselves."};
descriptions["29110"]={cn:"Dofus里剑齿虎的牙齿怎么会出现在月岛，还被人做成了项链？真有意思。",en:"No one knows how a Sabredon tooth necklace ended up on Moon Island. But it\'s impressive nonetheless!"};
descriptions["29111"]={cn:"穿上这件肩甲的人，最终都会被他们的爱人所吞噬，这应该能让你的邪恶派对增添一些趣味。",en:"Anyone who wears these epaulettes apparently ends up devoured by their lover, which should add some zest to your devilish parties."};
