descriptions["29113"]={cn:"佩戴这件护符时，能增强你对于未受过教育之人的影响力。成为他们的导师，引导他们走上正确的道路；也就是不要让他们走上你的路...",en:"Your influence over the unschooled grows when you wear this amulet. Be their guru and guide them on the right path; don\'t make them follow yours..."};
