descriptions["29115"]={cn:"这顶头盔相当之重，脱下时让你感到如释重负像要飞起来一般。别照字面意思去看，你不是只蝴蝶。",en:"This helmet is so heavy that when you take it off, you feel light and ready to take flight. Don\'t take it literally; you\'re not a butterfly yet."};
descriptions["29116"]={cn:"这顶头盔相当之重，脱下时让你感到如释重负像要飞起来一般。别照字面意思去看，你不是只蝴蝶。",en:"This helmet is so heavy that when you take it off, you feel light and ready to take flight. Don\'t take it literally; you\'re not a butterfly yet."};
descriptions["29117"]={cn:"出于某种神秘的原因，这条腰带让你感觉像羽毛一样轻盈。谁知道呢？如果你一直戴着它，你可能真的会开始相信这件事。",en:"For some mysterious reason, this belt makes you feel light as a feather. Who knows? If you keep wearing it, you may actually start to believe it\'s true."};
