descriptions["29119"]={cn:"传说这双靴子属于一位势不可挡的超级英雄，一位真正的钢铁人，现在正等待着正统继承者的到来。别再盯着看了，快去找那位继承者吧！",en:"Legend has it that these boots once belonged to an unstoppable superhero, a real ironman, and are now awaiting the arrival of his rightful heir. So quit staring at them and go find the heir, already!"};
descriptions["29120"]={cn:"即便是最强大的魔族，也要惧怕这护符。据说这护符上寄宿着一股古老的力量，可以消灭任何人事物。",en:"Even the most powerful Shushus fear this amulet, which is said to be inhabited by an ancient force that can annihilate anyone and anything."};
