descriptions["29130"]={cn:"你觉得这副肩甲会跟你说话，来填补你生活中的空虚；一边是天使的声音、另一边是魔鬼的声音。\n又或者，你可能只是疯了。",en:"You get the feeling that these epaulettes are talking to you to fill the empty spaces in your life. An angel\'s voice on one side, and a devil\'s on the other.\nAlternatively, you might just be going insane."};
