descriptions["29139"]={cn:"非常适合你下一次化妆舞会的装扮，会给你带来令人惊异的气息，让接近的美女们为之昏厥！（字面意思）\n不过要注意，它很难脱掉。",en:"Perfect for your next masquerade soirée, this headgear will give you incredible breath that will have all the cuties fainting at your approach. Literally!\nCareful, though, as it\'s surprisingly difficult to take off."};
