descriptions["29143"]={cn:"当注视着这枚戒指时，你开始对一切产生质疑，生、死...这一切究竟有什么意义？到了最后，当然，一切都不复存在...只有一片虚空。",en:"As you look at this ring, you begin to question everything. Life, death... what\'s the point of it all? In the end, of course, nothing remains... only the void."};
