descriptions["29146"]={cn:"穿上这双靴子是要付出代价的，无论你看到什么，都会解读出令人不安的清晰迹象。你刚从一个不相干的笔记上，想起下周要在岳母家吃晚饭。",en:"Equipping these boots comes at a cost. Indeed, you\'ll start interpreting unmistakably disturbing signs wherever you look. On an unrelated note, you\'ve just remembered you\'re having dinner at your mother-in-law\'s next week."};
