descriptions["29164"]={cn:"曾属于一名传奇设计师。BenK 总是能提出原创而有时令人不安的概念，对可能的风险有着非常独到的见解。这是他参加了无数次地狱拳所表现出来的性格特征，而那可并不总是能归类为“全年龄”的。 时而保守、时而随意，他在十二世界的环境中留下了无可否认的痕迹，他一手进行了许多关乎整个酷洛宇宙未来的修复工程。",en:"This cap once belonged to a legendary architect. Always suggesting original and sometimes disturbing concepts, BenK had a really strong appetite for risk. This is a personality trait that manifested itself during the countless times he participated in the Hellfists, the outcome of which could not always be categorized as \"for all ages\". Sometimes reserved, sometimes casual, he left an undeniable mark on the environments of the World of Twelve, and he single-handedly carried out many restoration projects that the future of the whole Krosmoz depended on."};
