descriptions["29167"]={cn:"有没有想过如果能回到过去，改变历史上的一个特定时刻，现今的十二世界会是什么样子？\n现在这个世界可不算多美好。",en:"Have you ever imagined what the World of Twelve would look like today if you could go back and change one specific moment in history?\nThis world might not be nearly as impressive."};
