descriptions["29169"]={cn:"这条腰带是从另一个时代过来的，似乎是由一个疯狂的科学家所留下。经常听到他一些毫无意义胡言乱语的科学术语，“2.21 吉瓦？！2.21 吉瓦...我怎能这么粗心？！”",en:"This belt seems to have come straight from another time. It was seemingly left by a mad scientist who could often be heard gibbering scientific jargon that made no sense like, \"2.21 gigowatts?! 2.21 gigowatts... How could I have been so careless?!\""};
