descriptions["29171"]={cn:"不要被巨大的犄角所迷惑，这顶头盔是为了保护你的私人空间，不是用来装东西。对手不会敢靠近你和你这令人印象深刻的犄角。",en:"Don\'t be fooled by the enormous horn; this helmet is made to preserve your personal space, not for charging. Opponents won\'t dare come near you and your impressive horn... hopefully."};
