descriptions["29179"]={cn:"曾属于一名嗜血的开膛手，持续地寻找新的受害者。他的恶行使他与恶魔越渐相似，直到最终成为了恶魔。",en:"Yew was a bloodthirsty executioner, always on the lookout for new victims. His vices gradually brought him closer to the demons, until he eventually became one himself."};
