descriptions["29205"]={cn:"由一名心碎的制甲师制作，他的爱人向着未知的土地展开了遥远的旅途，装饰在上面的许多宝石代表了他等待爱人的年数。等到爱人终于回来时，她已经不再是她了；一个恶魔占据了她的灵魂。男人出于爱，不顾一切地将自己的灵魂出卖给兀枢，只为了与真爱重逢，结果被转化为恐惧魔族，永远被一个充满怨恨的恶魔所附身。",en:"These epaulettes were made by a broken-hearted armorer. The many precious stones that adorn it represent the number of years he spent waiting for his beloved, who had left on an expedition to unknown lands. When she finally returned, she was no longer the same, as a demon had taken possession of her soul. Out of love, the man desperately agreed to sell his soul to Rushu to be reunited with his true love, and was transformed into a Horridemon to be possessed for all eternity by a demon consumed by resentment."};
