descriptions["29208"]={cn:"据说原主人与现在寄宿其中的恶魔签下了契约，如果戴在脖子上太久，可能会发狂并被杀戮的冲动所支配。也许应该在为时已晚之前丢掉它...",en:"They say that this amulet\'s original owner made a pact with a demon who now resides within it. If you keep it around your neck for too long, you may go quite mad and be overcome with murderous impulses. Perhaps you should get rid of it before it\'s too late..."};
