descriptions["29217"]={cn:"只要看一眼这顶头盔，挡在路上的敌人就会知道他们时日（或着说，分秒）无多了。",en:"One look at this headgear, and any unfortunate enemies who stumble across your path will know their days (or rather, minutes) are numbered."};
