descriptions["29219"]={cn:"大概是有史以来最棒的戒指了。",en:"This ring may just be the greatest of all time."};
descriptions["29220"]={cn:"大概是有史以来最棒的戒指了。",en:"This ring may just be the greatest of all time."};
descriptions["29221"]={cn:"奎特鲁斯一直认为，身为一个可怕的怪物这件事，并不是无法把自己打理好看的理由。你又有什么资格反驳他呢？",en:"Crateros always believed that being a dreadful monster was no reason he couldn\'t look nice. And who are you to contradict him?"};
descriptions["29222"]={cn:"奎特鲁斯一直认为，身为一个可怕的怪物这件事，并不是无法把自己打理好看的理由。你又有什么资格反驳他呢？",en:"Crateros always believed that being a dreadful monster was no reason he couldn\'t look nice. And who are you to contradict him?"};
descriptions["29223"]={cn:"这条腰带属于一位菲卡的狂热信徒，她对问题的敏锐眼光有时会让她陷入棘手的境地，但这并无碍于她足够熟练、强大并且坚持不懈的事实，也让人欢迎她作为队友。她敏锐而务实的头脑，使她成为我们这个时代最伟大的思想家之一。",en:"This belt belongs to a fervent disciple of Feca. Her sharp eye for problems sometimes gets her into tricky situations, but that doesn\'t change the fact that she\'s good enough, she\'s strong enough, and doggone it, people like her as an ally. Her keen and pragmatic mind have made her one of the greatest thinkers of our time."};
