descriptions["29226"]={cn:"这顶头盔属于属于一位菲卡的狂热信徒，他喜欢吃胡萝卜，并会在空闲时间把无数的力场放在他能找到的所有地方。然而，他的音乐品味仍有待改进，这就是为什么这款头盔会盖住佩戴者的耳朵。我们能怪谁呢？?",en:"This helmet belongs to a fervent disciple of Feca. He loves eating cawwots and, in his free time, placing countless glyphs wherever he can find room. His musical tastes leave something to be desired, however, which is why this helmet covers the wearer\'s ears. But who are we to judge?"};
