descriptions["29229"]={cn:"这件披风属于一位当代的传奇，那人不是最老练、也不是最有洞察力的人，但他有着无与伦比的坚毅与韧性。他总是正面迎接每一个面临的挑战，这也是他最终能够取得胜利并赢得他人认可的原因。",en:"This cape belongs to an absolute legend of the Wakfu era. He wasn\'t the most skilled or the most perceptive, but his tenacity was unmatched. He always met every challenge he faced, which is how he was eventually able to achieve victory and win the approval of others."};
descriptions["29230"]={cn:"这件披风属于一位当代的传奇，那人不是最老练、也不是最有洞察力的人，但他有着无与伦比的坚毅与韧性。他总是正面迎接每一个面临的挑战，这也是他最终能够取得胜利并赢得他人认可的原因。",en:"This cape belongs to an absolute legend of the Wakfu era. He wasn\'t the most skilled or the most perceptive, but his tenacity was unmatched. He always met every challenge he faced, which is how he was eventually able to achieve victory and win the approval of others."};
descriptions["29231"]={cn:"为了制作这件幸运护符，花费了数小时的工作投入。佩戴的人会发现自己在爱情中很幸运，只要他们记得祝护符的制作者生日快乐。",en:"Countless hours of work went into creating this good-luck amulet. Whoever wears it will find themselves lucky in love, as long as they remember to wish the amulet\'s creator a happy birthday."};
