descriptions["29241"]={cn:"你从那些可怜的恶魔那里抢走了这个护身符；很显然对他们没有帮助，只是一个无用的小饰品。",en:"You snatched this amulet from one of those poor demons, and it clearly didn\'t help them. It\'s just another useless trinket."};
descriptions["29242"]={cn:"你从那些可怜的恶魔那里抢走了这个护身符；很显然对他们没有帮助，只是一个无用的小饰品。",en:"You snatched this amulet from one of those poor demons, and it clearly didn\'t help them. It\'s just another useless trinket."};
descriptions["29243"]={cn:"有许多人担任过 Pro Doosers 公会的负责人，而西格玛是其中最杰出和最称职的人。他是一位出色的领导者，偶尔会因神秘的不适而瘫痪，像是无法回答有关欧萨莫达的任何问题之类的。希望他喜欢这枚戒指，甚至可能会给制作它的工匠一笔丰厚的奖金...谁知道呢。",en:"Plenty of Twelvians have served as head of the Pro Doosers\' guild, and Sigma still counts among the most illustrious and deserving of their number. He was an excellent leader who was occasionally crippled by enigmatic illnesses, like a strange inability to answer any question about Osamodas. Let\'s hope he enjoys this ring. Who knows, he might even give a nice fat bonus to the artisan who crafted it..."};
descriptions["29244"]={cn:"他是狂眼憎恨的化身，诅咒所有胆敢踏入他领土的冒险者。过去曾经有一位全身穿着绿衣、承载了英雄精神的年轻冒险者，与他进行了一场史诗般的战斗，而他在那场战斗中失去了这副肩甲。",en:"Orf is the reincarnation of Dementya\'s hatred, who curses all adventurers who dare enter his territory. He lost these traditional \"galon\"-style epaulettes in an epic battle against a young adventurer clad all in green who bears the spirit of the hero."};
descriptions["29245"]={cn:"你真的想不起来，是怎么会把这可怕东西穿到身上的。它有时会和你说话，内容可能有意义也可能毫无意义，其中以后者居多。",en:"You really can\'t remember what possessed you to put this awful thing on your body. It starts talking to you at times, about everything and nothing at all. Mostly the latter."};
