descriptions["29254"]={cn:"偶尔，会诞生彼此相连的残祟眼。这将是场你死我亡的地狱般战斗的开始，因为他们都无法忍受对方的存在，而最后剩下的就是这副肩甲了。所以当你认为你的家人很糟糕时，穿上这副肩甲好好想想吧。",en:"Once in a while, twin Reman\'haunts are born conjoined to one another. This is the start of a hellish battle that ends with them killing one another, since neither of them can stand the other\'s presence. These epaulettes are all that\'s left of them. So the next time you think your family is bad, wear these to put things in perspective."};
