descriptions["29257"]={cn:"维护这件胸甲的方式相当不寻常：每天的喂食要严格控制在 5 件胸甲和腰带，才能保持战斗状态！希望当你穿着它时，它不会有想吃零食的冲动...",en:"This breastplate requires its owner to keep up a rather unusual form of maintenance: a strict diet of 5 breastplates and belts per day to stay in fighting shape! Hopefully it won\'t get the urge for a snack while you\'re wearing it..."};
