descriptions["29260"]={cn:"迷路的冒险者有时会将此护符用作指南针，以免偏离道路。并无法保证这么做的效果，因为没有人找到过使用它的人。",en:"Lost adventurers sometimes try to use this amulet as a compass to avoid straying from their chosen path. Results are not guaranteed, however, as no one has ever found anyone who\'s used it."};
