descriptions["29263"]={cn:"有时当你感到孤独时，会发现自己正盯着这枚戒指。终于，有一个懂你的了。",en:"Sometimes when you\'re feeling lonely, you catch yourself looking this ring right in the eye. Finally, someone who understands you."};
