descriptions["29265"]={cn:"准备来一趟狂飙之旅 - 这双靴子有时会自行跑起来去吃昆虫或小动物。只要别开始跳舞就好...",en:"Get ready for a wild ride - these boots sometimes go running off on their own to snack on insects or small mammals. Just as long as they don\'t start dancing..."};
