descriptions["29267"]={cn:"这是一条会说话的腰带，通常会说着像是“嘿...我知道这里有个捷径。就在这边，看到没？相信我。”这样的话。别太相信它，否则可能会遇到讨厌的惊喜。",en:"This belt has the power of speech, and will often say things like, \"Hey, psst... I know a shortcut through here. Just right over here, see? Trust me.\"  Don\'t put too much confidence in its suggestions, or you could be in for a nasty surprise."};
