descriptions["29279"]={cn:"这神秘的物品似乎寄宿着某种邪恶的存在。经常会听到它低语着“什么，又输了？你又丢了弹珠，老朋友！”",en:"This mysterious headgear seem to be inhabited by some evil presence. You\'ll often hear it whispering sweet nothings like \"What, lost again? You\'re losing your marbles, old pal!\""};
