descriptions["29281"]={cn:"无论下雪、下雨或下冰雹，都无碍于这顶头盔在任务中对你的防护。有人甚至认为，这顶头盔还能让你走到自己头上。",en:"Neither snow nor rain nor sleet nor hail shall stop this helmet from protecting you on your appointed missions. Some even say that when you equip it, you can literally walk on your head."};
