descriptions["29283"]={cn:"这件护符的意义是什么？我们是谁、从何处来、又将去往何方？如果你曾经问过自己这些问题，你就只是一个正常的、有思想的人。如果没有...也许就不是。",en:"What is the meaning of this amulet? Who are we, where do we come from, and where are we going? If you ever ask yourself these questions, you\'re just a normal, thoughtful person. If not... maybe not."};
