descriptions["29291"]={cn:"你手中这件披风，属于十二世界中最冷静的潘达旺女神信徒之一。他体贴、富有创造力和好奇心，并不吝分享自己的知识，总是乐于帮助一路上遇到的冒险者。\n他可能没想到，其中一个人会为他制作这件披风以表示感谢。",en:"You hold in your hands a cloak that belonged to one of the World of Twelve\'s calmest disciples of Pandawa. Thoughtful, creative and curious, he shared his knowledge and was always happy to help the adventurers he met along the way.\nHe probably never expected that one of them would make him this cloak to express their thanks."};
