descriptions["29295"]={cn:"这双运动凉鞋，会让你的敌人有恐惧感。",en:"Sporting these sandals will give your enemies a sense of dread."};
descriptions["29296"]={cn:"比格斯廷克是一个著名的冒险家，探索过十二世界许多的洞穴。却在探索月岛的任务中失踪。",en:"Biggs Tinker was a popular adventurer who explored many caves around the World of Twelve. He disappeared on a mission to Moon Island."};
descriptions["29297"]={cn:"无论有多强壮，你都无法搬动或挥舞它；正如字面所说，它乃是不屈不挠的。",en:"No matter how strong you are, you\'ll never succeed in moving or wielding it. It is literally unyielding."};
