descriptions["29299"]={cn:"根据定义，一个数学常数不会改变。生活依然有趣，是因为尽管有着严格的规则，但你可以看到每时每刻都有新的事情发生。“有些事情永远不会改变”这句话会不断受到挑战。",en:"A mathematical constant, by definition, does not change. Life is still interesting because despite its rigid rules, you can see that something new happens at every moment in time. The saying \"some things never change\" simply needs to be constantly challenged."};
