descriptions["29301"]={cn:"这件吊带裤的持有者很少输掉战斗，他既强大又老练，多年来没有人能够击败他。他甚至花时间训练和教导对手，以便他们有一天可以超越他，但从来没有人做到过。",en:"The wearer of these overalls rarely lost a fight. He was so powerful and skilled that no one was able to defeat him for years. He even spent time training and teaching his opponents so that they might surpass him one day, but no one ever managed it."};
