descriptions["29310"]={cn:"朋友曾试图警告你，半夜在小巷里遇到的所谓的魔族造型师，不可能会把你的最大利益放在心上。下次，在星期四晚上点八品脱啤酒之前，最好三思。",en:"Your friends had tried to warn you that a so-called Shushu hairstylist that you met in an alley in the middle of the night clearly wouldn\'t have your best interests at heart. Next time, think twice before ordering that eighth pint on a Thursday night."};
