descriptions["29327"]={cn:"似乎有某人或某物寄宿其中，你发誓你在深夜里听到它说：“Bill Ding，你到底是怎么了？这孩子彻底完了！”真是精神折磨，还有这见鬼的“Bill Ding”到底是谁？",en:"It seems to be inhabited by someone or something. Late at night, you could swear you\'ve heard it say: \"Bill Ding, what in the world is wrong with you? The boy\'s completely destroyed!\" Totally traumatizing. And who the heck is \"Bill Ding\"?"};
