descriptions["29332"]={cn:"当你披上时，遇到的每个人都会喊道：“北方之王！愿王的统治长久！”你不明白为什么，但很令人享受。只是要小心，不要被冲昏了头脑。",en:"When you equip this cloak, everyone you meet cries out, \"The King in the North! Long may he reign!\" You don\'t understand why, but it\'s pretty enjoyable. Just be careful you don\'t let it go to your head."};
