descriptions["29337"]={cn:"制作这件胸甲的工匠，同时也是一名企业家和卓越的昆虫学者。他从研究中汲取灵感，制作出这件胸甲；能够以自然而有效的方式吓跑敌人，胸甲的涂漆设计让整体看起来像捕食者，也很像蝴蝶的翅膀。注意：不要穿来飞行。",en:"The artisan and entrepreneur who created this breastplate was also an entomologist par excellence. He took inspiration from his research to create a breastplate that would scare his enemies off in a natural and efficient way with painted designs made to look like predators, much like butterflies\' wings. Note: Do not attempt to fly wearing this."};
descriptions["29338"]={cn:"制作这件胸甲的工匠，同时也是一名企业家和卓越的昆虫学者。他从研究中汲取灵感，制作出这件胸甲；能够以自然而有效的方式吓跑敌人，胸甲的涂漆设计让整体看起来像捕食者，也很像蝴蝶的翅膀。注意：不要穿来飞行。",en:"The artisan and entrepreneur who created this breastplate was also an entomologist par excellence. He took inspiration from his research to create a breastplate that would scare his enemies off in a natural and efficient way with painted designs made to look like predators, much like butterflies\' wings. Note: Do not attempt to fly wearing this."};
descriptions["29339"]={cn:"卡哈巴尔想穿点什么装扮时，会缠上这条腰布，虽然也遮盖不了什么。即使如此，这还是一条不错的腰布。",en:"K\'abah\'al likes to wear this loincloth when he wants to dress up a bit. Unfortunately, it doesn\'t cover much. But still, it\'s a really nice loincloth."};
