descriptions["29343"]={cn:"用卡巴哈尔权杖的一部份所制作的戒指，有时它把你朋友点燃时会听到它咯咯地笑。",en:"This ring was passed down from K\'abah\'al, and was made from part of his scepter. You\'ll occasionally catch it giggling as it sets your friends on fire."};
