descriptions["29345"]={cn:"据说这双靴子让那些留着胡须的老疯子能够在湖面上行走，那为什么不把水变成啤酒呢？",en:"They say that these boots enabled some bearded old nutcase to walk on the surface of the Ch\'Tyx. Why not turn the water into beer while you\'re at it?"};
