descriptions["29350"]={cn:"小古飞是一名高博球员，以狂野的发色闻名，而非他的运动能力；然而球迷们很爱他，甚至给他起了个绰号叫“红纳度”。",en:"Gufetto was a gobbowl player better known for his wild hair color than his athletic prowess. The fans loved him, though, and followers of his team even nicknamed him Red-naldinho."};
descriptions["29351"]={cn:"小古飞是一名高博球员，以狂野的发色闻名，而非他的运动能力；然而球迷们很爱他，甚至给他起了个绰号叫“红纳度”。",en:"Gufetto was a gobbowl player better known for his wild hair color than his athletic prowess. The fans loved him, though, and followers of his team even nicknamed him Red-naldinho."};
