descriptions["29353"]={cn:"这是件属于 Suspect 的斗蓬，他是一名难以捉摸的布拉克玛狂战士。这名战士开设了布拉克玛最伟大的酒馆之一，那里欢迎着各种各样的人。\n尽管这名狂战士体格易虚，但他会为了改善朋友的日常生活而积极提出想法，见过他的人都能很快与他交上朋友。",en:"This clock belongs to an elusive Brakmarian Sacrier. This warrior founded one of Brakmar\'s greatest taverns, a welcoming place for Twelvians of every kind.\nDespite his fragile constitution, he was positively bursting with ideas to improve his friends\' daily lives. Anyone who\'s met him considers him a fast friend."};
descriptions["29354"]={cn:"这是件属于 Suspect 的斗蓬，他是一名难以捉摸的布拉克玛狂战士。这名战士开设了布拉克玛最伟大的酒馆之一，那里欢迎着各种各样的人。\n尽管这名狂战士体格易虚，但他会为了改善朋友的日常生活而积极提出想法，见过他的人都能很快与他交上朋友。",en:"This clock belongs to an elusive Brakmarian Sacrier. This warrior founded one of Brakmar\'s greatest taverns, a welcoming place for Twelvians of every kind.\nDespite his fragile constitution, he was positively bursting with ideas to improve his friends\' daily lives. Anyone who\'s met him considers him a fast friend."};
descriptions["29355"]={cn:"无论穿着这双靴子到何处，你肯定都能获得帮助。",en:"Wherever these boots take you, you can be sure you\'ll be supported for life."};
descriptions["29356"]={cn:"无论穿着这双靴子到何处，你肯定都能获得帮助。",en:"Wherever these boots take you, you can be sure you\'ll be supported for life."};
descriptions["29357"]={cn:"此肩甲制作时被浸泡在植物淬取物中，这将导致穿著者感到茫然但快乐。",en:"These epaulettes have been soaked in plant extract, which causes the wearer to become dazed but merry."};
descriptions["29358"]={cn:"这个护身符不会给你带来好运，它只是一条绳子绑上羽毛和一根骨头。虽然还不错。",en:"This charm won\'t bring you luck; it\'s just a piece of string with a feather and a bone. It\'s quite nice though."};
descriptions["29361"]={cn:"这条附肢的功用是什么？用来抓痒？行走？戳？捏？\n有些问题永远没有答案，心怀感激吧。",en:"What caused this appendage to appear? The need to tickle? Walk? Itch? Pinch?\nSome questions will forever remain unanswered. Be grateful."};
descriptions["29362"]={cn:"水果？蔬菜？谁知道呢！总之当地的魔族喜欢它。（是的，不管你相信与否，他们确实会喜欢些什么...）",en:"Fruit? Vegetable? Who knows! But the locals love it. (Yes, believe it or not, the locals do love something...)"};
descriptions["29363"]={cn:"这是瓦尔恩西亚的残留物，它试图在你睡觉时与你的潜意识交谈来腐化你。例如，它可能会低声说：“说真的，如果你跳出窗外，我会付你 50 卡玛...”",en:"This residue of Vaal\'Enthia tries to corrupt you by talking to your subconscious while you sleep. For example, it might whisper, \"Honest, I\'ll totally pay you 50 kamas if you jump out the window...\""};
descriptions["29364"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few drops should suffice."};
descriptions["29365"]={cn:"这种恶魔产物非常适合擦拭各种东西。\n甚至可以清除最顽强的污渍，例如敌人在厨房里留下的血迹。",en:"This demonic growth is great for wiping up all kinds of things.\nIt\'ll take care of even the toughest stains, like the pools of blood your enemies left all over your kitchen."};
descriptions["29366"]={cn:"握住这只手给你一种奇怪的感觉。",en:"Shaking this hand will give you a strange feeling in the pit of your stomach."};
descriptions["29367"]={cn:"据说坚不可摧、永不磨损。",en:"It\'s supposedly indestructible and never wears out."};
descriptions["29368"]={cn:"尽管外表令人惊异，但这只爪子并不危险。",en:"Despite its startling appearance, this claw is not dangerous."};
descriptions["29369"]={cn:"这是阿尔南的头骨，空的。很扯吧？",en:"This is Ar\'Nan\'s skull. Empty. Crazy, right?"};
descriptions["29370"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few drops should suffice."};
descriptions["29371"]={cn:"说最后一次，大伙们，不能用它来做培根。",en:"For the last time, people, you can\'t make bacon out of it."};
descriptions["29372"]={cn:"你在不知道这是什么的情况下，从地上捡到了它。这样对你来说可能比较好。",en:"You picked this up off the ground without really knowing what it was. It\'s probably better that way."};
descriptions["29373"]={cn:"别想着能用这来飞。",en:"Do not attempt to fly with this."};
descriptions["29374"]={cn:"尽管外观令人恶心，但这条触手能做成非常棒的烤肉串。",en:"Despite its unappetizing appearance, this tentacle makes an excellent shish kebab."};
descriptions["29375"]={cn:"奎特鲁斯特别喜欢用他那吓人的钩子活剥受害者。",en:"Crateros particularly enjoys flaying his victims alive with his impressive hook."};
descriptions["29376"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few drops should suffice."};
descriptions["29377"]={cn:"你后悔将这面罩从它的主人脸上撕下来，面罩下的样子要糟糕得多。",en:"You regret having torn this from its old owner\'s face. What was under the mask was far worse."};
descriptions["29378"]={cn:"仿佛在指着些什么。",en:"It seems to be trying to point something out to you."};
descriptions["29379"]={cn:"小心拿好。",en:"Handle with care."};
descriptions["29380"]={cn:"你总是觉得...狂眼正看着你！",en:"You always feel like... Dementya\'s watching you-u-u!"};
descriptions["29381"]={cn:"你来，你见，你征服；但你还是念不出那见鬼的名字。",en:"You came, you saw, you conquered, but you still can\'t pronounce that freaky name."};
descriptions["29382"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few drops should suffice."};
descriptions["29383"]={cn:"不太确定怎么来的，但干得好。",en:"Not really sure how you managed to get hold of this, but nice work."};
descriptions["29384"]={cn:"在营火旁度过舒适的夜晚时，当做完美的枕头。",en:"Makes an excellent pillow for those cozy nights around the campfire."};
descriptions["29385"]={cn:"寄宿着神秘的力量。",en:"This arm seems to be inhabited by a mysterious force."};
descriptions["29386"]={cn:"别将自己做为代价交出去 - 有的仅会是破灭结局。",en:"Don\'t offer them your own in exchange - it\'ll only end in tears."};
descriptions["29387"]={cn:"别指望用这块权杖尖创造奇迹。首先，你就不是一个魔法师。",en:"Don\'t expect to work miracles with this piece of a scepter. You\'re not much of a magician in the first place."};
descriptions["29388"]={cn:"有经验的牧民不辞辛劳地将这种粘稠的物质收集到小瓶子里，只要几滴就能起作用。",en:"An experienced trapper toiled tirelessly to collect the sticky substance contained in this flask! A few drops should suffice."};
