descriptions["29404"]={cn:"在人前炫耀这对翅膀，可能会让你满嘴羽毛。",en:"You might end up spitting feathers if you keep flaunting these fabulous wings in front of people."};
descriptions["29405"]={cn:"施加一层所有遗物的状态。",en:"Applies one level of all vestige states."};
descriptions["29406"]={cn:"我们都知道这个障碍的作用就是阻止人们破坏它另一边的事物。",en:"The barrier we all know and love for its ability to stop people breaking on through to the other side."};
descriptions["29407"]={cn:"据说在古老失传的语言中，“小麦”原本是别的字。",en:"Some say that in an ancient lost tongue, the word for \"wheat\" was originally \"cheh\"."};
descriptions["29408"]={cn:"你不知道是什么仪式，你只想穿漂亮的衣服，参加盛大的活动。",en:"You have no idea what the ceremony involves; you just want to wear beautiful clothes and attend grandiose events."};
descriptions["29409"]={cn:"这件绝美的服装，是度过了难忘的十年沃土时代的奖励。\n由 dracaplha#2705 所设计。",en:"This utterly beautiful costume serves as a reward for a memorable decade spent in the Wakfu Era.\nIt was designed by dracaplha#2705."};
descriptions["29410"]={cn:"直到今天，仍然没有人知道这名异常强大的恶魔是如何从正义骑士的看管下逃脱的。末日真是真是太神奇了...",en:"To this day, nobody knows how this exceptionally powerful demon managed to escape the Justice Knight\'s vigilance. It\'s just amazing what the Eliocalypse can lead to..."};
descriptions["29411"]={cn:"这把钥匙可以解锁植种、虚空、恐惧、巨眼以及坏灭地下城的一个乱入石碑等级。",en:"This key can be used to unlock an Intervention Stele level in the Phytomorph, Voidivion, Horridemon, Streye, and Destroyer dungeons."};
