descriptions["29454"]={cn:"女武神会在战斗结束后出现，将战死的英雄引导到英勇竞技场，他们可以在那里进行永恒的战斗。",en:"Valkyrs appear after battles and guide the heroes who fell in battle to the Arena of the Valiant where they can fight for eternity."};
descriptions["29455"]={cn:"你不知道穿过这个传送门的手指，最终会去往何方，但它看起来温暖而诱人。",en:"You don\'t know where the finger that goes through this portal will end up, but it seems warm and inviting."};
descriptions["29456"]={cn:"根据它的外观和异样，你很快就会意识到这个假龙蛋肯定是来自一名魔族。虽然不知道是怎么回事，但有一只恶魔的灵魂在其中，密切地观察着外面的世界。蛋壳上有着恶魔的眼睛，让它可以看见和窥探一切。有时你会听到被困住的魔族传来的耳语。",en:"Based on its appearance, and its deformity, you very quickly realize that this fake Dofus most certainly comes from a Shushu. Although it\'s not known how, one of these demons\' souls is contained within it, and it closely scrutinizes the outside world. Its eyes, grafted to the walls of the egg, allow it to see and spy on everything. You can sometimes hear whispers coming from the captive Shushu."};
descriptions["29457"]={cn:"许多科学家试图弄清楚兀枢到底有多强大，但谁也没有想到，他的力量竟然是无限的。有点像你，我猜。",en:"Many scientists tried to figure out just how powerful Rushu was. No one had yet figured out that his power was limitless. A bit like you, I guess."};
descriptions["29458"]={cn:"许多科学家试图弄清楚兀枢到底有多强大，但谁也没有想到，他的力量竟然是无限的。有点像你，我猜。",en:"Many scientists tried to figure out just how powerful Rushu was. No one had yet figured out that his power was limitless. A bit like you, I guess."};
descriptions["29459"]={cn:"当你感到疲乏和困倦时，戴上这顶头盔会是个不错的提神方式。",en:"Wearing this helmet is an excellent remedy when you\'re feeling wrung out and hung over."};
descriptions["29460"]={cn:"当你感到疲乏和困倦时，戴上这顶头盔会是个不错的提神方式。",en:"Wearing this helmet is an excellent remedy when you\'re feeling wrung out and hung over."};
descriptions["29461"]={cn:"兀枢亲手制作了这件披风，用来抵御来自背后的攻击。而你现在获得了它，但却没有任何生灵敢从背后...或从正面攻击你。",en:"This cloak was forged by Rushu himself as protection from attacks from behind. You\'ve inherited it, but no living soul would dare attack you from behind... or from the front for that matter."};
descriptions["29462"]={cn:"兀枢亲手制作了这件披风，用来抵御来自背后的攻击。而你现在获得了它，但却没有任何生灵敢从背后...或从正面攻击你。",en:"This cloak was forged by Rushu himself as protection from attacks from behind. You\'ve inherited it, but no living soul would dare attack you from behind... or from the front for that matter."};
descriptions["29463"]={cn:"当你的对手听到你的脚步声时，他们会开始向仇恨与毁灭之神祈祷——也就是你。",en:"When they hear your footsteps, your opponents will start to pray to the god of hatred and destruction, who is none other than yourself."};
descriptions["29464"]={cn:"当你的对手听到你的脚步声时，他们会开始向仇恨与毁灭之神祈祷——也就是你。",en:"When they hear your footsteps, your opponents will start to pray to the god of hatred and destruction, who is none other than yourself."};
descriptions["29465"]={cn:"无法用不割伤手臂的方式穿脱，但反正你也不需要手臂就能摧毁对手。",en:"It is impossible to put on or take off without cutting your arms. But it\'s not like you need your arms to destroy your opponents."};
