descriptions["29467"]={cn:"我们不知道这条护符代表什么，但有一点是肯定的：如果它属于兀枢，那对你的对手来说就不会是好兆头。",en:"We don\'t know what this amulet represents, but one thing is certain: If it belonged to Rushu, it doesn\'t bode well for your competition."};
