descriptions["29528"]={cn:"从兀枢宫殿所偷出的这枚戒指，会让所有的恶魔都为之颤抖！很恶魔，对吧？",en:"Stolen from Rushu\'s Palace, this ring will have all the demons in a flutter! Demonic, isn\'t it?"};
descriptions["29529"]={cn:"从兀枢宫殿所偷出的这枚戒指，会让所有的恶魔都为之颤抖！很恶魔，对吧？",en:"Stolen from Rushu\'s Palace, this ring will have all the demons in a flutter! Demonic, isn\'t it?"};
descriptions["29530"]={cn:"这条腰带被骗子的灵魂诅咒了，现在会在最糟糕的时机脱掉佩戴者的衣服，譬如你向老板要求加薪的时候。",en:"This belt was cursed by a trickster spirit and now it has a real tendency to drop its wearer\'s clothing at the worst possible moment, like just when you\'re about to ask your boss for a raise."};
descriptions["29531"]={cn:"这条腰带被骗子的灵魂诅咒了，现在会在最糟糕的时机脱掉佩戴者的衣服，譬如你向老板要求加薪的时候。",en:"This belt was cursed by a trickster spirit and now it has a real tendency to drop its wearer\'s clothing at the worst possible moment, like just when you\'re about to ask your boss for a raise."};
descriptions["29532"]={cn:"这是一个受诅咒的神奇蛋...据说它具有治愈严重伤害的惊人的特性。",en:"Now here\'s an intriguing cursed egg... They say that it has astonishing properties and can heal very serious injuries."};
descriptions["29533"]={cn:"这是一个受诅咒的神奇蛋...据说它具有治愈严重伤害的惊人的特性。",en:"Now here\'s an intriguing cursed egg... They say that it has astonishing properties and can heal very serious injuries."};
descriptions["29534"]={cn:"先警告你，它要戴五个晚上，每天五次！",en:"You were warned, though. It\'s to be worn for five nights, five times per day!"};
descriptions["29535"]={cn:"先警告你，它要戴五个晚上，每天五次！",en:"You were warned, though. It\'s to be worn for five nights, five times per day!"};
descriptions["29536"]={cn:"这条腰带通过将大量巨大的尖刺抵在皮肤上来保持你的身材。确实非常痛苦，但也非常有效。",en:"This belt keeps you in shape by sticking loads of huge spikes into your skin. Very painful, true, but also very effective."};
descriptions["29537"]={cn:"这条腰带通过将大量巨大的尖刺抵在皮肤上来保持你的身材。确实非常痛苦，但也非常有效。",en:"This belt keeps you in shape by sticking loads of huge spikes into your skin. Very painful, true, but also very effective."};
descriptions["29538"]={cn:"这顶头盔曾经戴在一只走失绵球的头上，至少故事是这样说的。他毫无迹象地突然出现在这片恶魔的土地上，从那以后，他有时会在梦中旅行，寻找他的田野。",en:"This helmet once adorned the head of a lost gobball, or so the story says. He appeared suddenly in demon lands without any special signs. Since then, he sometimes travels in his dreams searching for the fields that made up his estate."};
descriptions["29539"]={cn:"这顶头盔曾经戴在一只走失绵球的头上，至少故事是这样说的。他毫无迹象地突然出现在这片恶魔的土地上，从那以后，他有时会在梦中旅行，寻找他的田野。",en:"This helmet once adorned the head of a lost gobball, or so the story says. He appeared suddenly in demon lands without any special signs. Since then, he sometimes travels in his dreams searching for the fields that made up his estate."};
descriptions["29540"]={cn:"被诅咒的弓箭手穿的的被诅咒的披风。",en:"The cursed cloak of a cursed Cra."};
descriptions["29541"]={cn:"被诅咒的弓箭手穿的的被诅咒的披风。",en:"The cursed cloak of a cursed Cra."};
descriptions["29542"]={cn:"天资聪颖并不保证会拥有光明的未来，即使是这个世界上最聪明的人也受到了很大的折磨。",en:"Genius is no guarantee of a radiant future. The most enlightened in this world are also very tortured."};
descriptions["29543"]={cn:"天资聪颖并不保证会拥有光明的未来，即使是这个世界上最聪明的人也受到了很大的折磨。",en:"Genius is no guarantee of a radiant future. The most enlightened in this world are also very tortured."};
descriptions["29544"]={cn:"很明显，这次侦察任务走得太远了。",en:"A reconnaissance mission went a bit too far, clearly."};
descriptions["29545"]={cn:"很明显，这次侦察任务走得太远了。",en:"A reconnaissance mission went a bit too far, clearly."};
descriptions["29546"]={cn:"兀枢无所畏惧，也许除了他自己的力量。",en:"Rushu fears nothing, except maybe his own power."};
descriptions["29547"]={cn:"兀枢无所畏惧，也许除了他自己的力量。",en:"Rushu fears nothing, except maybe his own power."};
descriptions["29548"]={cn:"这胡须有某种魅力。",en:"This beard has a certain charm."};
descriptions["29549"]={cn:"很多人认为兀枢只是个传说，或至少他的力量被夸大了。现在你手中的这把钥匙，让你能够去证实那些故事有多么荒谬，因为暗影之王远比传说中要更强大。",en:"Many people thought that Rushu was just a myth or, at the very least, that the tales of his power were exaggerated. Now that you hold this key in your hands, you\'ll be able to verify just how misleading the stories are since the Lord of the Shadows is much stronger than the legends say."};
descriptions["29558"]={cn:"保护你的双脚免受潮湿和伤害的侵袭，但是对于高热却无能为力！",en:"The perfect footwear for all your cavernous adventures."};
descriptions["29559"]={cn:"向旁观者彰显你是个英勇的骑士，即便隐藏在盔甲底下的只是个抠脚汉。",en:"This helmet will give onlookers the impression that you\'re a valiant knight, even if underneath it you\'re just a big coward!"};
descriptions["29560"]={cn:"保护好勇士。",en:"Protects the chivalrous."};
descriptions["29561"]={cn:"当你身处异常狭窄的通道里的时候，这对护肩能完好地保护你。",en:"These super-sharp epaulettes double up as weapons for when you\'re in dire straits!"};
descriptions["29562"]={cn:"打开取得地下城排名的奖励！\n\n\n\n50% 机率取得一件外观物品\n\n100% 机率取得 3 份附魔碎片、奖章或重铸石\n\n3% 机率取得一个史诗或遗物升华",en:"Open it to find out what you\'ve won by being ranked among the best in the dungeon!\n\n50% chance of obtaining a cosmetic item\n100% chance of obtaining 3 sets of shards, tokens, or transmutations\n3% chance of getting an epic or relic Sublimation"};
descriptions["29563"]={cn:"打开取得地下城排名的奖励！\n\n\n\n50% 机率取得一件外观物品\n\n100% 机率取得 3 份附魔碎片、奖章或重铸石\n\n3% 机率取得一个史诗或遗物升华",en:"Open it to find out what you\'ve won by being ranked among the best in the dungeon!\n\n50% chance of obtaining a cosmetic item\n100% chance of obtaining 3 sets of shards, tokens, or transmutations\n3% chance of getting an epic or relic Sublimation"};
descriptions["29564"]={cn:"打开取得地下城排名的奖励！\n\n\n\n90% 机率取得一件外观物品\n\n100% 机率取得 6 份附魔碎片、奖章或重铸石\n\n5% 机率取得一个史诗或遗物升华",en:"Open it to find out what you\'ve won by being ranked among the best in the dungeon!\n\n90% chance of obtaining a cosmetic item\n100% chance of obtaining 6 sets of shards, tokens, or transmutations\n5% chance of getting an epic or relic Sublimation"};
descriptions["29566"]={cn:"人靠衣装才能威风。",en:"The clothes may not make the man, but they may make you a warrior."};
descriptions["29567"]={cn:"你现在可以穿得跟那位刽子手一样了。\n可以在阿斯图布酒馆将这间服装的部分版（仅有披风和帽子）换成这件完整版的服装。",en:"You can finally dress up as a butcher.\nThis costume can be traded in for the partial version (cape and hat only) at the machine in the Astrub Inn."};
descriptions["29568"]={cn:"用以解锁此一宠物造型。",en:"Can be used to unlock this pet skin."};
descriptions["29569"]={cn:"开发游戏有点像种树，这树枝可以种在阿斯图布的任何土壤中。\n可以在阿斯图布的导师兑奖机换成庇护袋的树枝。",en:"Ultimately, developing a game is a bit like planting a tree. This one can be planted in any soil in Astrub.\nThis cutting can be traded for haven bag cuttings at the mentor machine in Astrub."};
descriptions["29570"]={cn:"刚剪掉了树枝，它马上就长了回来，真神奇！如果把几棵结合起来，也许会更大。",en:"Right after you cut it, it begins to grow back. It\'s truly magic! Maybe if you combine several, yours will be even bigger."};
descriptions["29571"]={cn:"自从沃土时代开始以来，真是发生了许多事情！",en:"So much has happened since the start of the Wakfu Era!"};
descriptions["29572"]={cn:"自从沃土时代开始以来，真是发生了许多事情！",en:"So much has happened since the start of the Wakfu Era!"};
