descriptions["29579"]={cn:"美丽记忆，永久珍藏。",en:"A nice trophy for your personal collection."};
descriptions["29580"]={cn:"某些不该遗忘的事物已然消失。",en:"Some things that shouldn\'t have been forgotten have been lost."};
descriptions["29581"]={cn:"很难说这会给你带来好运还是厄运。\n可以肯定的是，它会让你的庇护袋里到处都是毛。",en:"It\'s hard to say if this will bring you good luck or bad.\nAll that\'s certain is that it will leave fur all over your Haven Bag."};
descriptions["29582"]={cn:"开发游戏有点像种树，这树枝可以种在庇护袋或公会领地。",en:"Ultimately, developing a game is a bit like planting a tree. This one can be planted in haven bags and haven worlds."};
descriptions["29583"]={cn:"美丽记忆，永久珍藏。",en:"A nice trophy for your personal collection."};
descriptions["29584"]={cn:"当你触摸这本日记时，会感到自己与无数的十二世界传说同在。",en:"When you touch this journal, you feel like you\'re vibing in harmony with countless Twelvian legends."};
descriptions["29585"]={cn:"打开取得终极首领排名的奖励！\n\n25% 机率取得一件外观物品\n100% 机率取得 2 组符文粉末、奖章或重铸石\n3% 机率取得遗物或史诗升华",en:"Open it to find out what you\'ve won by ranking against an Ultimate Boss!\n\n25% chance of obtaining a cosmetic item\n100% chance of obtaining 2 sets of shards, tokens, or transmutations\n3% chance of getting an epic or relic Sublimation"};
descriptions["29586"]={cn:"打开取得终极首领排名的奖励！\n\n50% 机率取得一件外观物品\n100% 机率取得 5 组符文粉末、奖章或重铸石\n12% 机率取得遗物或史诗升华",en:"Open it to find out what you\'ve won by ranking against an Ultimate Boss!\n\n50% chance of obtaining a cosmetic item\n100% chance of obtaining 5 sets of shards, tokens, or transmutations\n12% chance of getting an epic or relic Sublimation"};
descriptions["29587"]={cn:"打开取得终极首领排名的奖励！\n\n90% 机率取得一或两件外观物品\n100% 机率取得 8 组符文粉末、奖章或重铸石\n25% 机率取得遗物或史诗升华",en:"Open it to find out what you\'ve won by ranking against an Ultimate Boss!\n\n90% chance of obtaining one or two cosmetic items\n100% chance of obtaining 8 sets of shards, tokens, or transmutations\n25% chance of getting an epic or relic Sublimation"};
descriptions["29588"]={cn:"你得到这个奖章，是因为在不同角色拥有相同的服装。\n奖章可以在阿斯图布酒馆地下室的兑奖机那里，兑换成想要的服装。",en:"You were given this token because you learned the same costume with two different characters.\nIt can be exchanged for costumes of your choice at a machine under the Astrub Inn."};
descriptions["29589"]={cn:"根据定义，一个数学常数不会改变。生活依然有趣，是因为尽管有着严格的规则，但你可以看到每时每刻都有新的事情发生。“有些事情永远不会改变”这句话会不断受到挑战。",en:"A mathematical constant, by definition, does not change. Life is still interesting because despite its rigid rules, you can see that something new happens at every moment in time. The saying \"some things never change\" simply needs to be constantly challenged."};
descriptions["29590"]={cn:"根据定义，一个数学常数不会改变。生活依然有趣，是因为尽管有着严格的规则，但你可以看到每时每刻都有新的事情发生。“有些事情永远不会改变”这句话会不断受到挑战。",en:"A mathematical constant, by definition, does not change. Life is still interesting because despite its rigid rules, you can see that something new happens at every moment in time. The saying \"some things never change\" simply needs to be constantly challenged."};
descriptions["29591"]={cn:"此卷轴能附加一项效果于特定孔位组合的装备上。效果可叠加至 6 层。",en:"This scroll can be applied to a specific combination of sockets to add a single effect to an item. This effect can stack up to level 6."};
descriptions["29592"]={cn:"此卷轴能附加一项效果于特定孔位组合的装备上。效果可叠加至 6 层。",en:"This scroll can be applied to a specific combination of sockets to add a single effect to an item. This effect can stack up to level 6."};
