descriptions["29594"]={cn:"这把钥匙能用来进入魔之界终极次元裂缝进行战斗。",en:"This key can be used to start a fight in the ultimate rift in the Shustuft Crust."};
descriptions["29595"]={cn:"这块木头闻起来有股灰尘味，这正是魔之界的特色。",en:"This wood has a slightly ashy smell that is characteristic of the Shustuft Crust."};
descriptions["29596"]={cn:"你得到这个奖章，是因为在不同角色拥有相同的生物造型。\n奖章可以在阿斯图布酒馆地下室的兑奖机那里，兑换成想要的宠物或坐骑造型。",en:"You were given this token because you learned the same creature skin with two different characters.\nIt can be exchanged for mount or pet skins of your choice at a machine under the Astrub Inn."};
descriptions["29597"]={cn:"这把魔尘来自上古时代...并拥有惊人的效果！任何东西只要混进了它，就会在瞬间老化，很神奇吧？",en:"This powder might come from the Dofus Era... Its effects are surprising! It instantly ages anything it\'s mixed with. Magic, right?"};
descriptions["29598"]={cn:"打开取得地下城排名的奖励！\n\n100% 机率取得 3 份资源\n2% 机率取得一只宠物或一件升华",en:"Open it to find out what you\'ve won by being ranked among the best in the dungeon!\n\n100% chance of getting 3 sets of resources\n2% chance of getting a pet or a sublimation"};
