descriptions["29600"]={cn:"这件服装自有其聪明之处。",en:"This costume is actually intelligent, in its own way."};
descriptions["29601"]={cn:"你依然无法跟狐狸沟通，但至少可以模仿它们的外貌。",en:"You still can\'t talk to Kitsounes but at least you can copy their look."};
descriptions["29602"]={cn:"真的让你回到从前。",en:"This costume really takes you back."};
