descriptions["29616"]={cn:"这里是你的旅程终结之处。你一路以来的经历都有一个相同的目的：从奥古之乱中拯救十二世界。攀上泽尼特山不过是接下来一切的开端，许多冒险者攀上后从来没返回过。\n用这把钥匙前往泽尼特山巅，直面奥古，证明你正是这世界所期待的英雄。",en:"This is where your journey ends. Everything you\'ve been through so far has led you to the same objective: saving the World of Twelve from Ogrest\'s Chaos. Climbing Mount Zinit was just a taste of what\'s to come, because many adventurers have never returned.\nUse this key to reach the Mount Zinit Summit and face Ogrest to prove you\'re the hero this world is waiting for!"};
descriptions["29617"]={cn:"从泽尼特山收集五个钥匙碎片，制作泽尼特山巅的钥匙。",en:"Collect the five key fragments from Mount Zinit to make the Mount Zinit Peak key."};
descriptions["29618"]={cn:"从泽尼特山收集五个钥匙碎片，制作泽尼特山巅的钥匙。",en:"Collect the five key fragments from Mount Zinit to make the Mount Zinit Peak key."};
descriptions["29619"]={cn:"从泽尼特山收集五个钥匙碎片，制作泽尼特山巅的钥匙。",en:"Collect the five key fragments from Mount Zinit to make the Mount Zinit Peak key."};
