descriptions["29621"]={cn:"你在抓住奥古时扯下了这搓毛发，还记得吗？\n奥古随后痛打了你一拳，显然就是那一拳让你忘记有被痛打过。",en:"You got this clump of hair while grappling with Ogrest, don\'t you remember?\nHe gave you a good whack on the head in return. It goes without saying that that whack is probably why you don\'t remember your whack."};
descriptions["29622"]={cn:"能否助你拯救过去及未来的一切事物呢？",en:"Can this sword help you save everything that was and will be?"};
descriptions["29623"]={cn:"能否助你拯救过去及未来的一切事物呢？",en:"Can this sword help you save everything that was and will be?"};
descriptions["29624"]={cn:"无比强大的神剑，据说曾一度将两个世界分开后再合并起来。",en:"This sword is so powerful that it is said to have once separated and then reunited two worlds."};
descriptions["29625"]={cn:"无比强大的神剑，据说曾一度将两个世界分开后再合并起来。",en:"This sword is so powerful that it is said to have once separated and then reunited two worlds."};
descriptions["29626"]={cn:"这把武器以奇特的技术制作而成，不禁好奇奥古是从哪里拿到的。",en:"A strange technology seems to have crafted these weapons. You might wonder where Ogrest got his hands on it."};
descriptions["29627"]={cn:"这把武器以奇特的技术制作而成，不禁好奇奥古是从哪里拿到的。",en:"A strange technology seems to have crafted these weapons. You might wonder where Ogrest got his hands on it."};
descriptions["29628"]={cn:"这把铲子有两个功用：为敌人挖坟墓，以及确保他们永远在里面。",en:"This shovel can be used for two things: digging small graves for your enemies, and making your enemies stay there forever more."};
descriptions["29629"]={cn:"这把铲子有两个功用：为敌人挖坟墓，以及确保他们永远在里面。",en:"This shovel can be used for two things: digging small graves for your enemies, and making your enemies stay there forever more."};
descriptions["29630"]={cn:"在夜里会更略微闪亮，能够照亮你的道路，并且指引怪物找到你。",en:"It shines a little brighter at night, so it will light your way and guide all the monsters in the area toward you."};
descriptions["29631"]={cn:"在夜里会更略微闪亮，能够照亮你的道路，并且指引怪物找到你。",en:"It shines a little brighter at night, so it will light your way and guide all the monsters in the area toward you."};
descriptions["29632"]={cn:"根据来自另一个世界的传说，这是一把强大而神圣的武器，用来保护宇宙免受浑沌与巨人的侵害。如果你能举起这把锤子，就能好好教训奥古一顿。",en:"According to a legend from another world, this magical hammer is an ultra-powerful divine weapon. It is used to protect the universe from chaos and especially from giants. That should teach Ogrest a lesson, if you can even lift the thing."};
descriptions["29633"]={cn:"根据来自另一个世界的传说，这是一把强大而神圣的武器，用来保护宇宙免受浑沌与巨人的侵害。如果你能举起这把锤子，就能好好教训奥古一顿。",en:"According to a legend from another world, this magical hammer is an ultra-powerful divine weapon. It is used to protect the universe from chaos and especially from giants. That should teach Ogrest a lesson, if you can even lift the thing."};
descriptions["29634"]={cn:"由古人所遗留下来的智慧结晶，但即使是最伟大的贤者，也无法抚平和止住奥古的悲伤。",en:"This staff is a remnant of the wisdom of the ancients, but not even the greatest of sages could have soothed and contained Ogrest\'s sorrow."};
descriptions["29635"]={cn:"由古人所遗留下来的智慧结晶，但即使是最伟大的贤者，也无法抚平和止住奥古的悲伤。",en:"This staff is a remnant of the wisdom of the ancients, but not even the greatest of sages could have soothed and contained Ogrest\'s sorrow."};
descriptions["29636"]={cn:"从这把弓射出的箭会在沿途留下一道光线，无畏的航海人必备。",en:"Arrows shot from this bow leave a ray of light floating behind them, so it\'s a must-have for intrepid navigators."};
descriptions["29637"]={cn:"从这把弓射出的箭会在沿途留下一道光线，无畏的航海人必备。",en:"Arrows shot from this bow leave a ray of light floating behind them, so it\'s a must-have for intrepid navigators."};
descriptions["29638"]={cn:"这副卡牌有着强大的力量，即使不作弊也依然能嬴。",en:"These magical cards are so powerful that you can stop cheating and you\'ll still win."};
descriptions["29639"]={cn:"这副卡牌有着强大的力量，即使不作弊也依然能嬴。",en:"These magical cards are so powerful that you can stop cheating and you\'ll still win."};
descriptions["29640"]={cn:"远古魔杖有个迷人的特点，如果将它用作咖啡搅拌棒，不仅风味更佳，甚至还会在奶泡上留下图案，像是爱心、星星或啾啾。任何有实力的咖啡师都该有一根。",en:"The age-old wand has a fascinating characteristic. If you use it as a makoffee stirrer, not only will your drink taste better, but the wand will even leave a little drawing in the cream, such as a heart, a star, or a piwi\'s head. It\'s a must for all baristas worthy of the name."};
descriptions["29641"]={cn:"远古魔杖有个迷人的特点，如果将它用作咖啡搅拌棒，不仅风味更佳，甚至还会在奶泡上留下图案，像是爱心、星星或啾啾。任何有实力的咖啡师都该有一根。",en:"The age-old wand has a fascinating characteristic. If you use it as a makoffee stirrer, not only will your drink taste better, but the wand will even leave a little drawing in the cream, such as a heart, a star, or a piwi\'s head. It\'s a must for all baristas worthy of the name."};
descriptions["29642"]={cn:"这根指针转过的圈比你吃过的米还多，当然，这是指如果你懂得算数的话。",en:"This clock hand has been around the block more times than you can count. Assuming you know how to count, of course."};
descriptions["29643"]={cn:"这根指针转过的圈比你吃过的米还多，当然，这是指如果你懂得算数的话。",en:"This clock hand has been around the block more times than you can count. Assuming you know how to count, of course."};
descriptions["29644"]={cn:"灵感可以是一个想法、影响或启发，并最终化为创作。灵感有时出现地很突然，有时又难以捉摸，并且有时会在你意想不到的时候出现，甚至可能会隐藏在你意想不到的地方。有些人有自己沉思的方法，而其它务实或学术的人有他们坚持的方法。灵感不可避免地会受到自身经验的影响，因此当你做着看似简单但却不习惯的事时，是难以发现它的，只会让你楞在空白的页面（或画布）前，感到自己非常愚蠢。\n无论如何，重点在于画石头并不容易。",en:"Inspiration can be an idea, an influence, or an illumination that leads to creation. Sometimes it\'s sudden, sometimes it\'s elusive, sometimes it appears when you\'re not expecting it, and it can hide where you would never have thought to find it. Some have their muses, while other more pragmatic and scholarly people stick to their own methods. It is inevitably influenced by your experience, so finding it in a seemingly simple task that you\'re not accustomed to doing can be difficult, enough so to make you feel quite stupid in front of a blank page (or drawing).\nAnyway, the point is that drawing rocks isn\'t so easy."};
descriptions["29645"]={cn:"尽管这把神器年代久远，但归于尘土的只会是你在冒险旅途中遇到的敌人。",en:"Despite this artifact\'s age, the only things that will turn to dust are the enemies you\'ll meet on your adventure."};
descriptions["29646"]={cn:"尽管这把神器年代久远，但归于尘土的只会是你在冒险旅途中遇到的敌人。",en:"Despite this artifact\'s age, the only things that will turn to dust are the enemies you\'ll meet on your adventure."};
descriptions["29647"]={cn:"与樱桃树近似的品种，只在春节期间出现。据说许愿后把护身符挂上树枝，愿望就会实现。这树枝可以种在庇护袋或公会领地。",en:"A species akin to cherry trees, these trees only appear during the Spring Has Sprung festival. It is said that if you make a wish and hang a talisman from its branches, it will come true. This cutting can be planted in haven bags and haven worlds."};
descriptions["29648"]={cn:"边跑边将所有人扫开。",en:"You\'ll sweep everyone away with this run."};
descriptions["29649"]={cn:"你会给十二世界的人们树立一个理想，让他们会追逐你的背影。他们会绊倒、会跌倒，但当时候到了，他们会和你一起沐浴在阳光下。到时候，你将帮助他们创造奇迹。",en:"You\'ll give the people of the World of Twelve an ideal to reach. They\'ll run after you, they\'ll stumble, and they\'ll fall. But when the time comes, they\'ll join you in the sunshine. When the time comes, you\'ll help them perform miracles."};
descriptions["29650"]={cn:"我的剑是我的真爱。类似的剑还有很多，但这一把是我的。",en:"My sword is my true love. There are lots of similar swords out there, but this one is mine."};
descriptions["29651"]={cn:"很难说这会给你带来好运还是厄运。\n可以肯定的是，它会让你的庇护袋里到处都是毛。",en:"It\'s hard to say if this will bring you good luck or bad.\nAll that\'s certain is that it will leave fur all over your Haven Bag."};
